{
  "Format": "2.0.0",
  "ConfigSchema": {
    "BilingualMode": {
      "AllowValues": "true, false",
      "Default": "true"
    }
  },
  "Changes": [
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/ExtraDialogue",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "SummitEvent_Dialogue1_Spouse": "I was just thinking about the last %year years... / 我在回想过去的 %year 年……",
        "PurchasedItem_1_QualityLow": "Hey, {0}. / 嘿，{0}。#$b# So I stopped by Pierre's the other day and bought {1} {2}. It was the first time I've seen one of those there in a while...  / 因此，我几天前去了趟皮埃尔那，买了{2}。这是我第一次看到那些东西……#$b#I cooked it up for dinner last night... It filled the house with a {3} odor. I don't even want to know where Pierre found that thing.$s / 我昨晚将其制成了晚餐……整个房间里充满了{3}气味。我甚至不想知道皮埃尔在哪找到了那东西。$s#$e# Anyways... / 无论如何……",
        "Farm_RobinWorking2": "Your new {0} will be ready in {1} days. I'm going to be working on this thing day and night! / 你的新{0}将在 {1} 天内完工。我将夜以继日的扑在这件事上！",
        "Town_DumpsterDiveComment_Adult": "Hey, Stop that! ...Yuck!$s / 嘿，别碰那些垃圾！……很脏！$s",
        "SummitEvent_closingmessage4": "We've been watching every step of the way / 我们见证了你征途中的每一步……",
        "SummitEvent_Dialogue3_Sam": "I feel like I've changed a lot from when we first met... you know? / 自从我们相遇以来，我改变了许多……你感觉到了吗？#$b#...you might call it 'maturity'... hehe.$10 / ……你可能会说我“变成熟了”……嘿嘿。$10#$b#But I'm at a place, now, where I'm actually really excited about our future together...$l / 但是在此时此地，我更加期待我们共同的未来……$l#$b#Even if that means just doing normal stuff, like... uh... buying groceries and changing diapers... hah...$10 / 哪怕只是做些稀松平常的事情，像是……呃……采购日用品和换尿布……哈……$10",
        "PurchasedItem_5_VegetableOrFruit": "I bought the tastiest {2} from Pierre's shop the other day.  / 前几天，我从皮埃尔的商店买了最美味的{2}。#$b#He said that he grew the thing in his own backyard. I didn't know Pierre was such a talented farmer!$h / 他说，他在自己后院种植那个东西。我没想到皮埃尔是这样一个能干的农民！$h#$b#Looks like you might have some competition, huh? / 看起来你们之间可能有竞争，对吧？",
        "PurchasedItem_1_QualityHigh_Willy": "Hey, {0}. / 你好呀，{0}。#$b# So I stopped by Willy's the other day and bought {1} {2}. I've never seen one so fresh!  / 那天我路过威利的店，买了个{2}。真的是超级新鲜！#$b#So I cooked it up for dinner last night, and it filled the house with a {3} smell.. It was a hit!$h / 然后我昨晚拿它做了晚餐，屋子里满是{3}的味道……真的超棒！$h#$b#He told me you caught it yourself... I'm impressed! / 他告诉我是你自己抓到的……真了不起！#$e# Anyways... / 总之呢……",
        "Gunther_MuseumComplete": "The museum looks amazing! Thanks again for all your help. / 博物馆看起来太棒啦！再次感谢你的帮助。",
        "Morris_WeekendGreeting_MembershipAvailable": "Welcome to JojaMart! How is your weekend going? / 欢迎来到 Joja 超市！周末过得怎么样？#$b#Membership is now available! With a Joja Membership, you'll be able to make improvements in the community with the help of our dedicated personnel... for a fee, of course. / 会员资格现已上市！成为 Joja 会员，在专职人员的帮助下，您将能够付费改进社区……当然。#$b#Oh, and another thing... Mayor Lewis promised us that if anyone else joined up, he'd let us turn that old community center into a Joja Warehouse. Isn't that wonderful?#$q -1 -1#Membership costs {0}g. Well, would you like to join us?#$r -1 -1 Yes#Yes.#$r -1 -1 No#No. / 啊，还有另一件事……镇长刘易斯向我们承诺，如果其他任何人加入了，就让我们把旧的社区中心变成 Joja 仓库。那不是好极了？#$q -1 -1#会员费用 {0} 金。那么，你愿意加入我们吗？#$r -1 -1 Yes#愿意。#$r -1 -1 No#不愿意。",
        "PurchasedItem_2_QualityHigh_Jodi_Willy": "Hi... did you sell {1} {2} to the fish shop the other day? I think I bought it... / 嗨……前些日子你是不是卖了{2}给鱼店？大概是我买下的……#$e#It was pretty high-quality stuff. Very firm meat. / 那鱼的品质相当不错。鱼肉很紧实。",
        "SummitEvent_Dialogue3_Sebastian": "Before I met you, I spent most of my time turned away from reality... because I thought I'd never find happiness. / 在遇到你之前，我把自己的人生都耗费在逃避现实上……因为我觉得自己永远都得不到幸福。#$b#...but you've shown me that the world isn't such a dark place, after all.$h\"/faceDirection Sebastian 3/pause 500/speak Sebastian \"...That's one of the reasons I love you...\" / ……但你向我证明，世界并不只是一片黑暗。$h\"/faceDirection Sebastian 3/pause 500/speak Sebastian \"……我有许多爱你的理由，这是其中之一……\"",
        "PurchasedItem_2_QualityHigh": "Hi... did you sell {1} {2} to the general store the other day? I think I bought it... / 嗨……你前几天向杂货店出售了{2}吗？我好像把它买了下来……#$e#It was pretty high-quality stuff. I'm impressed. / 这是品质相当高的东西。给我的很印象深刻。",
        "Birdie15": "Fruit, fish, and foraged food... It's a good diet! I feel as healthy as ever. / 水果、鱼、采集到的食物……吃得真不错！我感觉跟以前一样健康。",
        "SummitEvent_Dialogue1_Lewis": "You know, @... I've been mayor of Pelican Town for a long time. / @啊……我担任鹈鹕镇镇长已经有很长时间了。#$b#People have come and gone. We've lived through times of hardship, and times of plenty. / 有人来了，也有人走了。我们共同经历过苦难，也经历过富足。",
        "Spouse_MonstersInHouse": "Um... Honey? Why are there monsters in the house? / 呃……亲爱的？为什么房子里有怪物？",
        "SummitEvent_closingmessage2": "You challenged yourself to reach the summit / 你挑战自己，登上了顶峰。",
        "Birdie2": "If you're ever feeling queasy in the stomach, a bite of ginger does wonders, dear... / 如果你感觉胃不舒服，吃一口姜会有奇效，孩子……",
        "Island_willy_rescue": "Are you okay? I found you washed up on the shore, lad.$s / 小伙子你没事吧？你被冲到了岸上，是我找到你的。$s^Are you okay? I found you washed up on the shore, miss.$s / 小姑娘你没事吧？你被冲到了岸上，是我找到你的。$s#$b#You really had me worried... I thought you were a goner! Be a little more careful out there...$s / 我太担心了……我以为你快没气了！在外面要小心一点啊……$s#$b#The island can be a dangerous place. / 这个岛屿可不是到处都安全的。",
        "SummitEvent_Dialogue3_Penny": "We have a beautiful home and a thriving family... it's all I've ever dreamed of, and more.$l / 我们有漂亮的房子，有欣欣向荣的家……这已经超出我所梦想的一切了。$l",
        "Gunther_NoArtifactsFound": "Hello there! Welcome to the Stardew Valley Archaeological Office. / 你好啊！欢迎来到星露谷考古研究办公室。#$b#Uh... This is embarrassing, but the previous curator made off with the entire collection. We don't have any artifacts for display. / 啊……说起来怪丢人的，不过上一任馆长把所有的藏品都卷走了。我们什么可展示的工艺品也没有了。#$b#But I'm hoping to remedy that soon! Hey, if you find any artifacts or minerals out there... would you let me know? / 不过我希望这一点能很快得到改善！嘿，如果你在外面找到什么工艺品啊矿石啊之类的，能不能告诉我一声呢？",
        "Morris_CommunityDevelopmentForm_PlayerFemale": "$q -1 -1#I've got the Joja Community Development Form right here for you, miss. Care to take a look?#$r -1 -1 Yes#Yes#$r -1 -1 No#No / $q -1 -1#小姐，我为您拿到了 Joja 社区发展申请书。要看看吗？#$r -1 -1 Yes#是#$r -1 -1 No#否",
        "ProfessorSnail_Hint_827": "Long ago, a rare species of cave-bat made their home here. The evidence suggests they were adapted to tolerate intense heat. Interesting, huh? / 很久以前，一种罕见的洞穴蝙蝠栖息在这里。有证据表明它们能够耐受高温。很有趣对吧？",
        "SummitEvent_Dialogue3_Maru": "You've really accomplished a lot since you moved here, @. It's incredible.\"/pause 300/faceDirection Maru 3/pause 400/speak Maru \"I think it's safe to say that you were meant to be a farmer!$h\" / @，你自从搬到这里之后，真的做出了不少成就。实在是太了不起了。\"/pause 300/faceDirection Maru 3/pause 400/speak Maru \"我想，你应该生来就是当农场主的料！$h\"",
        "MisterQi_PlayerClubMember": "Well, well, well... Look who made it inside my exclusive clubhouse. / 终于见到你了，孩子，真好啊。欢迎来到我的专属会所。#$e#You've got the 'spark'... that's why I singled you out. / 你已经得到了“火花”……这就是为什么我挑中了你。#$e#What spark? Ah... The conduit of mystery, of art... / 什么火花？啊……就是通往神奇彼岸，通往艺术的通道……#$b#People like us have a responsibility to keep the world alive, to give folks a taste of the extraordinary. / 像我们这样的人有责任让世界保持活力，给乡亲们非凡的味道。#$e#You see, kid... The world's like a bowl of rice. It's got substance, but it ain't worth nothin' without a good, zesty sauce. That's where we come in. / 明白吗，小子……这个世界就像一碗饭。它有食材，但是如果没有好的、刺激的酱料，便索然无味。这就是为什么这个地方会存在。#$b#Didn't you ever wonder who put those treasure chests in the old mineshaft? I like to give people surprises. / 你难道不想知道是谁把那些宝箱放在老矿井里？我喜欢给人们惊喜。#$e#You'll understand someday. Just keep doing your best and never give up. / 总有一天你会明白的。尽力做到最好，永不放弃。",
        "NewChild_Adoption": "It's so wonderful to welcome little {0} into our life. / 小家伙走进我们的生活{0}真是太好了！",
        "Island_leo_rescue": "It seems like you're going to live.$u / 看来你还活着。$u#$b#My bird-friends spotted you and told me you were in danger, so I dragged you all the way down here.$s / 我的鸟儿朋友们发现了你，告诉我你有危险，所以我拖着你把你带到了这里。$s#$b#Please be safe out there. I don't want to be sad anymore...$s / 在外面还请多注意安全。我不想再伤心一次了……$s",
        "ProfessorSnail_Hint_825": "If you see something wiggling in the dirt, make sure to excavate it. You never know what might be under there! / 你要是看到土地里有什么东西在蠕动，别忘了把它挖出来看看。你永远猜不到地里究竟藏着什么的！",
        "PurchasedItem_Caroline_QualityLow": "Oh, @... This is embarrassing. I threw one of your {2}s you sold us into my compost bin.$s / 哦，@……好尴尬。我把你卖给我的{2}中的一个，扔进了堆肥箱。$s#$b#Now the whole thing smells horrendous. Where did you find that thing again? / 现在，那整个东西难闻极了。你是在哪找到那东西的？",
        "Birdie17": "The weather is warm and lovely year round, my dear... it feels perfect for me bones... / 孩子，这里的气候全年温暖宜人……很适合我这把老骨头……",
        "PurchasedItem_Haley": "Emily tried to serve me {1} {2} for dinner last night... I threw it away when she wasn't looking. / 昨晚，埃米莉想要把{2}作为我们的晚餐……我趁着她没看到的时候，把它扔掉了。#$e#I don't like health food...$s / 我不喜欢健康食品……$s",
        "Mines_PlayerKilled_Maru_Spouse": "...I found you unconscious in the mines. You were gone so long I started to get worried about you! / ……我发现你在矿山不省人事。你去了那么长时间，我开始担心起你来！#$b#Be a little more careful next time, okay?$s / 下次小心点，好吗？$s",
        "Town_DumpsterDiveComment_Teen": "Um... Why are you digging in the trash?$s / 呃……你在垃圾堆里面翻什么呢？$s",
        "SummitEvent_Intro2_Spouse": "It's so beautiful up here... / 这里真美……",
        "Clint_NoInventorySpace": "Hey. Your tool is ready but you don't have any room in your inventory. / 嘿。你的工具准备好了，但你的物品栏满了。",
        "Morris_FirstGreeting": "Welcome to JojaMart! How are you doing today? / 欢迎来到 Joja 超市！今天过得怎么样？#$b#We're currently in the process of setting up a brand-new membership system for our customers. Please check back soon to join! / 我们目前正在为客户建立一个全新的会员制。请稍后访问并加入我们！",
        "PurchasedItem_2_QualityHigh_Willy": "Hi... did you sell {1} {2} to the fish shop the other day? I think I bought it... / 我说……前些日子你把{2}卖给鱼店了吧？大概是我买下来了。#$e#It was pretty high-quality stuff. I'm impressed. / 这鱼的品质真的很好，我记得很清楚。",
        "PurchasedItem_3_QualityHigh_Rude_Willy": "I went shopping last night and picked up {1} {2} on sale for only {3}g. / 我昨晚去购物，用优惠价买了个{2}，只花了 {3} 金。#$e# It was actually pretty {4}. / 那东西确实挺{4}。",
        "PurchasedItem_2_QualityLow": "Hi... did you sell {1} {2} to the general store the other day? I think I bought it... / 嗨……你前几天向杂货店出售了{2}吗？我好像把它买了下来……#$e#The quality was decent. / 质量感觉很好。",
        "SummitEvent_Intro_Lewis": "Wow... Look at that view. / 哇……看看这光景。",
        "PurchasedItem_Caroline_QualityHigh": "Oh, @... This is embarrassing. I threw one of your {2}s you sold us into my compost bin.$s / 哦，@……好尴尬。我把你卖给我的{2}中的一个，扔进了堆肥箱。$s#$b#But on the bright side, the worms are really loving it! They've never looked happier! / 但是，从好的方面想，蠕虫喜欢极了！他们从没这么快乐过！",
        "PurchasedItem_1_QualityHigh": "Hey, {0}. / 嘿，{0}。#$b# So I stopped by Pierre's the other day and bought {1} {2}. It was the first time I've seen one of those there in a while...  / 因此，我几天前去了趟皮埃尔那，买了{2}。这是我第一次看到那些东西……#$b#I cooked it up for dinner last night... It filled the house with a {3} smell.. It was a hit!$h / 我昨晚将其制成了晚餐……整个房间里充满了{3}气味……非常成功！$h#$b#I'm glad Pierre's stock is starting to expand again. / 我很高兴皮埃尔的存货再次开始扩大。#$e# Anyways... /  无论如何……",
        "SummitEvent_closingmessage5": "And you've made us very proud! / 我们为你感到无比自豪！",
        "Morris_BuyMovieTheater": "Ah, our favorite customer... I have exciting news for you! Joja headquarters has approved the construction of a new Joja 'entertainment opportunity' to replace the nearby Joja Warehouse. We just need an investor willing to support our vision! So, naturally, I turn to you... our most devoted and generous Joja member. / 啊，我们最喜欢的顾客……我有激动人心的消息要告诉你！Joja 总部已经批准拆掉附近的Joja仓库，在那里建造一个新的 Joja “娱乐机会”。我们只需要一个愿意支持我们愿景的投资者！于是，我很自然地找到了您……我们最热诚慷慨的 Joja 会员。#$b#$q -1 -1#We could make this happen for a small investment of... *cough*... 500,000g...$h#$r -1 -1 Yes#Yes#$r -1 -1 No#No / $q -1 -1#我们只需要……咳咳……500,000 金的小额投资……就能实现它。$h#$r -1 -1 Yes#是#$r -1 -1 No#否",
        "Birdie28": "It's a full moon, tonight... Whether your fortune be good or bad, be on the alert, my dear... The spirits are restless. / 今晚是满月……孩子，不管你的运气是好是坏，提高警惕……鬼魂们躁动不安。",
        "Morris_FirstGreeting_CommunityCenterComplete": "Welcome to JojaMart! How are you doing today? / 欢迎来到 Joja 超市！您今天过得怎么样？#$b#Unfortunately, due to unforeseen circumstances our Joja Membership offer is not currently available. I'm certain it will get sorted out soon! / 很遗憾，由于意外情况，我们的 Joja 会员优惠目前无法提供。我相信很快就会解决的！",
        "SummitEvent_Intro2_Spouse_Gruff": "Great view, huh? / 风景不错，对吧？",
        "NewChild_FirstChild": "Everything went well, and now little {0} is part of the family. We're very fortunate. / 一切都很好，现在{0}小家伙是家里的一份子。我们真幸运。",
        "Mines_PlayerKilled_Spouse_PlayerMale": "You were gone so long I started to get worried about you! I started crying when I saw your limp body...$s / 你已经去了那么长时间，我不由得担心起你来！当我看到你柔弱的身体时，我哭了起来……$s",
        "PurchasedItem_3_QualityHigh_Rude": "I went shopping last night and picked up {1} {2} on sale for only {3}g. / 我昨晚去购物了，买了廉价出售的{2}，只需要{3}克。#$e# It was actually pretty {4}. / 它真是相当{4}。",
        "Robin_HouseUpgrade_Accepted": "Thank you! I'll get started tomorrow. I should be finished in around three days. / 非常感谢！我明天就开始。大约需要三天时间完成。",
        "Farm_RobinWorking1": "Your new {0} will be ready in {1} days. Just pretend I'm not here. / 你的新{0}将在 {1} 天内完工。假装我不在这里。",
        "Robin_PamUpgrade_Accepted": "That's so generous of you! I'll start working on the upgrade tomorrow. It should take around three days. / 你真慷慨！我明天就会开始升级。应会耗费三天左右时间。",
        "Robin_Instant": "This {0} is pre-fabricated, so there's no construction time! Convenient, isn't it?$h / 这个{0}是预制的，因此没有施工时间！方便吧！？$h",
        "Morris_ComeBackLater": "Come back tomorrow and we can see about getting some community improvements started... Just make sure to bring a lot of money. Hehe. / 明天再来，我们就开始着手社区整治……记得带上钱啊。呵呵。",
        "ProfessorSnail_Hint_822": "You know, I bet if you did some panning, you could find some interesting stuff in the nearby river. / 要我说，如果你用淘盘在附近的河里捞一捞，一定能发现些有意思的东西。",
        "Morris_StillProcessingOrder": "We're currently processing your last Community Development order. Please come back after the work is complete. / 目前，我们正处理您的最后一个社区发展需求。请完工后回来。",
        "Birdie19": "Have you seen the little banana altar in the jungle? If I had a banana I'd set it there and see what happens... heh heh...$h / 你在雨林里见过那个小小的香蕉祭坛吗？要是我拿到一根香蕉，我会把它摆上去看看会发生什么……呵呵……$h",
        "Morris_WeekendGreeting_SecondPlayer": "Welcome to JojaMart! How is your weekend going? / 欢迎来到 Joja 超市！周末过得怎么样？#$b#Hmm... Our records show that you live on a farm with some other folks... I'm sorry, but we can only sell a membership to the owner of your residence. / 嗯……我们的记录显示，你与其他人住在一个农场……我很抱歉，但是我们只能向您住所的业主出售会员资格。",
        "Gunther_NothingToDonate": "It doesn't seem like you have anything to donate to the museum. Better get out there and do some treasure hunting, huh? / 你似乎没有要捐给博物馆的。最好出去寻宝，哈？",
        "PurchasedItem_5_Cooking": "I bought the tastiest {2} from Pierre's shop the other day.  / 前几天，我从皮埃尔的商店买了最美味的{2}。#$b#He said he cooked the thing himself using local ingredients. I didn't know Pierre was such {3} {4} chef! / 他说，他使用本地配料，自己烹调了那东西。我没想到皮埃尔如此{3} {4}大厨！",
        "NewChild_SecondChild1": "Just look at our little family... We've come a long way, haven't we? / 看看我们的小窝……我们有了很大的进展，对吧？",
        "Sandy_PlayerClubMember": "What happened? You're a club member?! / 发生了什么？你是会员？",
        "PurchasedItem_4_Willy": "So I was at Willy's other day and he showed me {1} {2} you brought in. / 那天我在威利的店里，他给我看了你弄来的{2}。#$e#I cooked it up for dinner with some lemon and a side of rice pilaf. Pretty good!$h / 我拿它做了炒饭当晚餐，还配上了柠檬。真挺好吃的！$h",
        "SummitEvent_closingmessage": "It's been a long road... / 这是一条漫漫长路……",
        "SummitEvent_Dialogue2_Lewis": "But I have to say, in all the years I've been mayor, nothing has made me so proud as seeing %farm Farm blossom under your care.$h / 但我必须承认，看到%farm农场在你的照料下焕发生机，我心中是如此的骄傲，以至于在我担任镇长多年的见闻里，都挑不出其他事物能与之相比。$h#$b#You've taken the farm beyond the wildest dreams of your Grandfather. / 你的爷爷做梦也不会想到，你能够将农场建设成这个模样。#$b#And in the process, you've changed the valley forever. / 而在建设的过程中，你也永远地改变了星露谷。",
        "Mines_PlayerKilled_Maru_NotSpouse": "...I found you unconscious in the mines. I was hunting for minerals and I almost stepped on your head! / ……我发现你在矿山不省人事。我当时正在寻找矿产，差点踩在你头上！#$b#Be a little more careful next time, okay?$s / 下次小心点，好吗？$s",
        "Mines_PlayerKilled_Clint": "...I found you unconscious in the mines. I think I blew my back out, dragging you all the way up here. / ……我发现你在矿山不省人事。我以为我当时要累死了，一路上把你拖到这儿来！#$b#Be a little more careful next time, okay?$s / 下次小心一点，好吗？$s",
        "PurchasedItem_3_NonRude": "I went shopping last night and picked up {1} {2} on sale for only {3}g. / 我昨晚去购物了，买了廉价出售的{2}，只需要 {3} 金。#$e# I couldn't pass up that great price. / 我不能错过那么低的价格。",
        "ProfessorSnail_Hint_820": "Have you found any golden coconuts on the island? It's rumored that many interesting things can be found inside of them... / 你在岛上找到过金椰子吗？有传闻说，金椰子里有许多不错的东西……",
        "PurchasedItem_3_QualityLow_Rude_Willy": "I went shopping last night and picked up {1} {2} on a 'chum-bucket' sale for only {3}g. / 我昨晚去购物，在“海之霸”促销上买了个{2}，只花了 {3} 金。#$e# It was {4}! No wonder Willy was practically giving that {5} away... / 那真的是{4}！怪不得威利卖这{5}就像白送一样……",
        "PurchasedItem_Pierre_QualityHigh_Willy": "Ahoy! Remember that {2} you brought in the other day? Well, I sizzled it up in me cabin last night... / 你好啊！还记得你那天弄来的{2}吗？那啥，我昨晚在自家小屋里把它烧焦了……#$b#T'was the finest fish I've had since I was a wee lad!$h / 那真是自打小时候起我吃过的最好的鱼了！$h",
        "SummitEvent_Intro_Spouse": "Hey, @. / 嗨，@。",
        "Birdie23": "I've been here so long, I can't even hear the ocean anymore... / 在这里待了太久，我已经听不到海浪声了……",
        "Morris_WeekendGreeting_CommunityCenterComplete": "Welcome to JojaMart! How is your weekend going? / 欢迎来到 Joja 超市！您周末过得怎么样？#$b#Unfortunately, due to unforeseen circumstances our Joja Membership offer is not currently available. I'm certain it will get sorted out soon! / 很遗憾，由于意外情况，我们的 Joja 会员优惠目前无法提供。我相信很快就会解决的！",
        "SummitEvent_Intro_Morris": "Ah, @... My favorite Joja member. / 啊，@……我最喜欢的 Joja 会员。",
        "Morris_Greeting": "Welcome to JojaMart! How are you doing today? / 欢迎来到 Joja 超市！今天感觉如何啊？#$b#I don't believe we've met. I'm Morris, Joja Customer Satisfaction Representative. / 我们似乎是第一次见面。我叫莫里斯，是Joja的顾客满意度代表。#$b#When you decide you want to become a Joja Member, I'll be delighted to help make your transition a joyous experience. / 当你想要成为Joja成员时，我很乐意帮助你轻松地适应这里。",
        "Morris_PlayerSignedUp": "Excellent! Welcome to Joja Corporation! Come back tomorrow and we can see about getting started on some community development projects... Oh, and don't forget your wallet! Hehe. / 太棒了！欢迎来到 Joja 公司！明天再来吧，我们就可以开始着手社区整治了……哦，别忘了带上钱包！呵呵。#$b#Now, let me call Mayor Lewis and see about gutting that nasty old community center... / 现在，我来打个电话给镇长刘易斯，看看脏乱的老社区中心要怎么弄……",
        "Morris_FirstGreeting_MembershipAvailable": "Welcome to JojaMart! How are you doing today? / 欢迎来到 Joja 超市！今天过得怎么样？#$b#Membership is now available! With a Joja Membership, you'll be able to make improvements in the community with the help of our dedicated personnel... for a fee, of course. / 会员资格现已上市！成为 Joja 会员，在专职人员的帮助下，您将能够付费改进社区……当然。#$b#Oh, and another thing... Mayor Lewis promised us that if anyone else joined up, he'd let us turn that old community center into a Joja Warehouse. Isn't that wonderful?#$q -1 -1#Membership costs {0}g. Well, would you like to join us?#$r -1 -1 Yes#Yes.#$r -1 -1 No#No. / 啊，还有另一件事……镇长刘易斯向我们承诺，如果其他任何人加入了，就让我们把旧的社区中心变成 Joja 仓库。那不是好极了？#$q -1 -1#会员费用 {0} 金。那么，你愿意加入我们吗？#$r -1 -1 Yes#愿意。#$r -1 -1 No#不愿意。",
        "NewChild_SecondChild2": "Two beautiful children... We've come a long way, haven't we? / 两个漂亮的小孩……我们有了很大的进展，对吧？",
        "Birdie5": "I walk the beach every day to see if anything new has washed ashore. There's a lot floating around out there! / 我每天都在海滩上散步，看看有没有新东西冲上岸来。海面上可是漂浮着很多东西！",
        "Mines_PlayerKilled_Robin": "...I found you unconscious in the mines. I almost mistook you for a piece of exotic wood! / ……我发现你在矿山不省人事。我几乎把你错认为是一块热带木！#$b#Be a little more careful next time, okay?$s / 下次，更加小心一点，好吗？$s",
        "ProfessorSnail_Hint_826": "Hmm... My nose is telling me that snake spines might be found in the western region of the island. / 嗯……我能闻出来，这段蛇脊骨应该来自于岛的西侧。",
        "SummitEvent_Dialogue3_Leah": "I think we've both found what we were looking for in this place. / 我觉得，我们都在这里找到了自己想要的东西。#$b#I wouldn't want to be anywhere else, but here with you.$l / 除了于此时此地和你待在一起，我别无所求。$l",
        "Mines_PlayerKilled_Spouse_PlayerFemale": "You were gone so long I started to get worried about you! I almost had a heart attack when I saw your limp body...$a / 你已经去了那么长时间，我不由得担心起你来！当我看到你柔弱的身体时，我差点发心脏病……$a",
        "SummitEvent_Dialogue2_Spouse": "...But look how far we've come. / ……想想看，我们居然走了这么远。",
        "SummitEvent_Dialogue3_Shane": "If I hadn't met you, @... I might not even be here right now. / @，要是我没有遇见你……恐怕我就不会到这里来了。#$b#Which would be a shame, because the bird-watching up here is phenomenal!$h\"/emote farmer 16/pause 1000/speak Shane \"Heh... I... I tend to joke a lot, because...well...$s / 那就太可惜了，毕竟这里是绝无仅有的观鸟点！$h\"/emote farmer 16/pause 1000/speak Shane \"……我……我经常开玩笑，因为……呃……$s#$b#I guess keeping things light-hearted makes it so I don't have to open up and make myself vulnerable.\"/emote Shane 28/speak Shane \"But every season that goes by, with you, I get a little more comfortable with myself. / 我觉得，只要把所有事情都一笑置之，我就不用敞开心扉，让自己变得脆弱了。\"/emote Shane 28/speak Shane \"但与你在一起，每度过一个季节，我都会变得更加安然自在一些。#$b#Uh.. I guess what I want to say is... / 呃……我想说的大概就是……#$b#I have no regrets marrying you!$h\" / 和你结婚我无怨无悔！$h\"",
        "Morris_JojaCDConfirm": "Excellent! We'll get our workers on it tonight. It should be ready for you by tomorrow. / 太棒了！今晚我们将招聘工人。明天会为你准备好。",
        "Morris_FirstGreeting_SecondPlayer": "Welcome to JojaMart! How are you doing today? / 欢迎来到 Joja 超市！今天过得怎么样？#$b#Hmm... Our records show that you live on a farm with some other folks... I'm sorry, but we can only sell a membership to the owner of your residence. / 嗯……我们的记录显示，你与其他人住在一个农场……我很抱歉，但是我们只能向您住所的业主出售会员资格。",
        "Morris_TheaterBought": "Half a mil...!$2 / 五十万……！$2#$b#*Ahem*... I mean... Excellent! Our Joja Construction Team will begin work on the new building tonight! Thank you for supporting our work. / 咳……我是说……太好了！我们的 Joja 施工队今晚将开始新大楼的施工！感谢您对我们的工作的支持。",
        "SkullCavern_100_event_honorable": "clubloop/-100 -100/farmer 6 6 2 MrQi 10 7 0/specificTemporarySprite qiCave/removeQuest 30/viewport 10 7 true/pause 3500/speak MrQi \"Well, well, well... you made it.\"/pause 500/playSound boop/faceDirection MrQi 3 true/pause 50/faceDirection MrQi 2/pause 100/playSound boop/animate MrQi false false 100 0 1 2 3 3 3 2 1 0/pause 1500/speak MrQi \"Come closer, now... don't be shy.\"/emote farmer 40/playSound boop/pause 500/move farmer 0 4 1/move farmer 4 0 0/pause 500/stopJittering/speak MrQi \"I heard you were attempting a deep dive into these caverns today... / clubloop/-100 -100/farmer 6 6 2 MrQi 10 7 0/specificTemporarySprite qiCave/removeQuest 30/viewport 10 7 true/pause 3500/speak MrQi \"好、好、好……你做到了。\"/pause 500/playSound boop/faceDirection MrQi 3 true/pause 50/faceDirection MrQi 2/pause 100/playSound boop/animate MrQi false false 100 0 1 2 3 3 3 2 1 0/pause 1500/speak MrQi \"走近一些，马上……不要害羞。\"/emote farmer 40/playSound boop/pause 500/move farmer 0 4 1/move farmer 4 0 0/pause 500/stopJittering/speak MrQi \"我听说你今天正试图潜入这些洞穴……#$b#I had to see for myself!\"/animate MrQi false false 100 0 1 2 3 3 3 2 1 2 3 3 3 2 1 0/pause 1000/playSound boop/pause 1000/speak MrQi \"Impressive... very impressive. You passed my test with flying colors, kid. / 我必须亲眼看看！\"/animate MrQi false false 100 0 1 2 3 3 3 2 1 2 3 3 3 2 1 0/pause 1000/playSound boop/pause 1000/speak MrQi \"真开眼界……太开眼界了。孩子，你出色地通过了我的考验。#$b#I'm very pleased that you challenged yourself and came down the honorable way, instead of skipping all the levels by crafting staircases. / 我十分高兴地见到，你挑战自我，一路荣耀走来，没有通过制作楼梯跳过任何关卡。#$b#That shows you're the real deal, kid. You've got principles. / 这表明你是真材实料，孩子。你有原则。#$b#You understand the importance of challenging yourself, and holding yourself to the highest standard, even if no one is watching. / 你明白挑战自己的重要性，即使没有人注意，也要坚持自己的最高标准。#$b#That's why you're special, kid... see? You lead by example. I like that.\"/pause 500/speak MrQi \"Now... go over to the table and drink this special milk I've prepared for you.\"/pause 500/move farmer 3 0 0/move farmer 0 -1 0/emote farmer 8/speak MrQi \"It's called 'Iridium Snake Milk'... one healthy swig of that and you'll become even more powerful.\"/pause 1000/faceDirection farmer 2 true/specificTemporarySprite removeSprite 803/farmerEat 803/awardFestivalPrize qimilk/pause 2000/message \"The taste is awful, and the texture is even worse.\"/pause 100/pause 500/jump farmer/playSound reward/message \"... But your health is permanently increased by 25!\"/pause 1000/fade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 500/playSound boop/speak MrQi \"Good luck out there, kid.\"/pause 500/playSound boop/end / 这就是为什么你很特别，孩子……明白吗？你以身作则。我欣赏这点。\"/pause 500/speak MrQi \"现在……去桌边，喝下我给你准备这杯特殊奶汁。\"/pause 500/move farmer 3 0 0/move farmer 0 -1 0/emote farmer 8/speak MrQi \"这叫作“铱蛇牛奶”……喝一小口，你就会变得更加强大。\"/pause 1000/faceDirection farmer 2 true/specificTemporarySprite removeSprite 803/farmerEat 803/awardFestivalPrize qimilk/pause 2000/message \"味道很糟糕，口感则更差。\"/pause 100/pause 500/jump farmer/playSound reward/message \"……但你的健康值却永久增加了 25！\"/pause 1000/fade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 500/playSound boop/speak MrQi \"孩子，祝你在那儿好运。\"/pause 500/playSound boop/end",
        "SummitEvent_Outro_Morris": "I just want to say, @... I appreciate all the hard work you've done for Joja Co. / @，我只想说……非常感激你为 Joja 公司做的一切。#$b#Our strength comes from our members, and you've shown exemplary drive and ingenuity. It makes me proud to work for the company.$h / 我们仰仗着我们的会员才得以强大，而你展现出了教科书般的积极性与机巧。所以，我才会因为供职于这间公司而自豪。$h",
        "Robin_NewConstruction": "Okay, I'll start working on your new {0} first thing tomorrow morning!$h / 好吧，明天一早，我的第一件事就是着手造你的新{0}。$h",
        "SummitEvent_Dialogue3_Alex": "I've finally discovered who I want to be... and I feel certain about the future.\"/pause 500/speak Alex \"I don't think I would've gotten here without you, @.\" / 我终于明白了自己想要成为什么样的人……我对未来更有把握了。\"/pause 500/speak Alex \"@，如果没有你，我恐怕做不到这一切。\"",
        "PurchasedItem_2_QualityHigh_Jodi": "Hi... did you sell {1} {2} to the general store the other day? I think I bought it... / 嗨……你前几天向杂货店出售了{2}吗？我好像把它买了下来……#$e#It was pretty high-quality stuff. As soon as I smelled it I was back in Granny's old cottage... / 这是品质相当高的东西。当我闻到它，我好像回到了奶奶的老屋里……",
        "ProfessorSnail_Hint_821": "You know, there's some great fishing on this island. From what I know, many of the fish enjoy nibbling on ancient bones... / 其实，岛上有许多优质的钓鱼地点。据我所知，许多鱼都喜欢咬古老的骨头……",
        "SummitEvent_Dialogue3_Abigail": "Standing here, looking out on the horizon... I get a feeling of endless possibility. / 站在这里，眺望地平线……我能感受到无穷无尽的可能性。#$b#I'm just happy I get to explore this world, with you by my side...$l / 我很高兴，能有机会和你一起探索这个世界……$l",
        "PurchasedItem_Abigail_QualityLow": "Hey. We had one of those {2}s you sold at the shop for dinner last night... I guess it was starting to go bad and my Dad couldn't bear to throw it out.$h / 嘿。昨晚，我们买了一个你在商店出售的{2}做晚饭……我想它已开始变质了，我的爸爸舍不得扔掉。$h#$b#Unfortunately it tasted like {3}.$s / 不幸地是，它尝起来像{3}。$s",
        "Morris_CommunityDevelopmentForm_PlayerMale": "$q -1 -1#I've got the Joja Community Development Form right here for you, sir. Care to take a look?#$r -1 -1 Yes#Yes#$r -1 -1 No#No / $q -1 -1#先生，我为您拿到了 Joja 社区发展申请书。要看看吗？#$r -1 -1 Yes#是#$r -1 -1 No#否",
        "SummitEvent_Outro_Lewis": "You might not realize it, but I care a lot about this town, @. / @，也许你没有感觉到，我非常关心这个镇子。#$b#%year years ago, I was deeply worried about the future of the valley.$s / %year 年前，我非常担心星露谷的未来。$s#$b#But now, I feel completely at ease. / 但现在我彻底放心了。#$b#Who knew a humble farmer moving to town would change everything?$h / 谁又能想到，一位移居而来的普通农场主能够带来翻天覆地的变化呢？$h#$b#...Thank you. / ……谢谢你。",
        "Town_DumpsterDiveComment_Child": "Eww... What are you doing?$s / 呃……你在做什么？$s",
        "Robin_UpgradeConstruction_Festival": "Okay, I'll start working on your {1} upgrade the day after tomorrow. I always take festivals off.$h / 好吧，后天，我就开始给你的{1}升级。毕竟我还得放假呢。$h",
        "Clint_StillWorking": "Um, I'm still working on your {0}. It won't be ready today. / 嗯，我还在做你的{0}。今天是做不好了。",
        "PurchasedItem_Elliott": "I saw that Pierre had fresh {2} in the shop the other day! Marvelous. It smelled just perfect... and firm, too! / 前几天，我看到皮埃尔的商店里有新鲜的{2}！好极了。它闻起来真是完美……还很结实！",
        "PurchasedItem_4": "So I was at the store the other day and Pierre showed me {1} {2} you brought in. / 所以前几天，我在商店里，皮埃尔告诉我你买了{2}。#$e#I bought it.$h / 然后，我也买了它。$h",
        "Robin_NewConstruction_Festival": "Okay, I'll start working on your new {0} the day after tomorrow. I always take festivals off.$h / 好吧，后天，我就着手造你的新{0}。毕竟我还得放假呢。$h",
        "PurchasedItem_3_NonRude_Willy": "I went shopping last night and picked up {1} {2} on sale for only {3}g. / 我昨晚去购物，用优惠价买了个{2}，只花了 {3} 金。#$e# I couldn't pass up that great price. / 价格太实惠了，我没法放过。",
        "PurchasedItem_Teen": "Hey, so I picked up {2} at the store last night. My mom wanted something good for dinner. / 嘿，我昨晚在商店里买了一个你的{2}。我妈妈想买些好东西做晚餐。",
        "SummitEvent_closingmessage3": "What an accomplishment! / 多么了不起的成就！",
        "SummitEvent_Dialogue3_Elliott": "Heh... it just dawned on me...$h / 嘿……我突然意识到……$h#$b#We've reached the summit, but not just physically... metaphorically as well. / 现在我们不仅爬到了顶峰……而且在事业层面上也到达了顶峰。#$b#How poetic!$l / 真有诗意！$l",
        "Wizard_Hatch": "What are you doing? I only allow those I trust to enter there.   / 你正在做什么？我只允许我信任的那些人进来这里。 ",
        "Birdie22": "Hello, dear... you look healthy and in good spirits today!$h / 你好，孩子……看起来你今天很健康，心情也不错！$h",
        "SkullCavern_100_event": "clubloop/-100 -100/farmer 6 6 2 MrQi 10 7 0/specificTemporarySprite qiCave/removeQuest 30/viewport 10 7 true/pause 3500/speak MrQi \"Well, well, well... you made it.\"/pause 500/playSound boop/faceDirection MrQi 3 true/pause 50/faceDirection MrQi 2/pause 100/playSound boop/animate MrQi false false 100 0 1 2 3 3 3 2 1 0/pause 1500/speak MrQi \"Come closer, now... don't be shy.\"/emote farmer 40/playSound boop/pause 500/move farmer 0 4 1/move farmer 4 0 0/pause 500/stopJittering/speak MrQi \"I heard you were attempting a deep dive into these caverns today... / clubloop/-100 -100/farmer 6 6 2 MrQi 10 7 0/specificTemporarySprite qiCave/removeQuest 30/viewport 10 7 true/pause 3500/speak MrQi \"好、好、好……你做到了。\"/pause 500/playSound boop/faceDirection MrQi 3 true/pause 50/faceDirection MrQi 2/pause 100/playSound boop/animate MrQi false false 100 0 1 2 3 3 3 2 1 0/pause 1500/speak MrQi \"走近一些，马上……不要害羞。\"/emote farmer 40/playSound boop/pause 500/move farmer 0 4 1/move farmer 4 0 0/pause 500/stopJittering/speak MrQi \"我听说你今天正试图潜入这些洞穴……#$b#I had to see for myself!\"/animate MrQi false false 100 0 1 2 3 3 3 2 1 2 3 3 3 2 1 0/pause 1000/playSound boop/pause 1000/speak MrQi \"Impressive... very impressive. Making it all the way down here is quite a feat! / 我必须亲眼看看！\"/animate MrQi false false 100 0 1 2 3 3 3 2 1 2 3 3 3 2 1 0/pause 1000/playSound boop/pause 1000/speak MrQi \"真开眼界……太开眼界了。一路下来，是多么伟大的一个成就啊！#$b#...although you did skip a bunch of levels by crafting staircases. Clever, sure... but not very honorable.$1 / ……尽管你通过制作楼梯，跳过了一堆关卡。聪明，当然……但不是很光荣。$1#$b#Even so, it must have been a lot of work to mine all that stone. And that sort of dedication is praiseworthy. You're a rare one, kid.\"/pause 500/speak MrQi \"Now... go over to the table and drink this special milk I've prepared for you.\"/pause 500/move farmer 3 0 0/move farmer 0 -1 0/emote farmer 8/speak MrQi \"It's called 'Iridium Snake Milk'... one healthy swig of that and you'll become even more powerful.\"/pause 1000/faceDirection farmer 2 true/specificTemporarySprite removeSprite 803/farmerEat 803/awardFestivalPrize qimilk/pause 2000/message \"The taste is awful, and the texture is even worse.\"/pause 100/pause 500/jump farmer/playSound reward/message \"... But your health is permanently increased by 25!\"/pause 1000/fade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 500/playSound boop/speak MrQi \"Good luck out there, kid.\"/pause 500/playSound boop/end / 即便如此，对于我来说，要挖掘那么石头，也是一项大工程。这种专注是值得称赞的。你是件宝贝，孩子。\"/pause 500/speak MrQi \"现在……去桌边，喝下我给你准备这杯特殊奶汁。\"/pause 500/move farmer 3 0 0/move farmer 0 -1 0/emote farmer 8/speak MrQi \"这叫作“铱蛇牛奶”……喝一小口，你就会变得更加强大。\"/pause 1000/faceDirection farmer 2 true/specificTemporarySprite removeSprite 803/farmerEat 803/awardFestivalPrize qimilk/pause 2000/message \"味道很糟糕，口感则更差。\"/pause 100/pause 500/jump farmer/playSound reward/message \"……但你的健康值却永久增加了 25！\"/pause 1000/fade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 500/playSound boop/speak MrQi \"孩子，祝你在那儿好运。\"/pause 500/playSound boop/end",
        "PurchasedItem_1_QualityLow_Willy": "Hey, {0}. / 你好呀，{0}。#$b# So I stopped by Willy's the other day and bought {1} {2}. He said you caught it yourself!  / 那天我路过威利的店，买了个{2}。他说是你自己抓到的！#$b#I cooked it up for dinner last night... and, uh... It filled the house with a {3} odor. I don't even want to know where you found that thing...$s / 然后我昨晚拿它做了晚餐……那个，呃……屋子里满是{3}的味道。真的很糟糕，你是在什么鬼地方弄到的……$s#$e#Anyways... / 总之呢……",
        "Robin_UpgradeConstruction": "Okay, I'll start working on your {1} upgrade first thing tomorrow morning!$h / 好吧，明天一早，我的第一件事就是着手给你的{1}升级。$h",
        "Farm_RobinWorking_ReadyTomorrow": "Your new {0} will be finished tomorrow! Are you excited? / 你的新房子{0}明天完成！你兴奋吗？",
        "SeedShop_Abigail_Drawers": "Hey, don't even think about it! That's private!$a / 嘿，想都别想！这是隐私！$a",
        "SummitEvent_Dialogue3_Harvey": "When I'm next to you, I'm not even scared of falling off this cliff and dashing onto the sharp rocks below...$l\"/jump Harvey/shake Harvey 1000/pause 1000/speak Harvey \"...$8 / 有你在我身边，我就不会害怕从悬崖上摔下去，落在下面的锋利的石头上……$l\"/jump Harvey/shake Harvey 1000/pause 1000/speak Harvey \"……$8#$b#I... I love and admire you very much, @...$l\" / 我……我非常爱慕，而且崇敬你，@……$l\"",
        "PurchasedItem_Leah": "The other day I bought {1} {2} at Pierre's. It was perfect on a bed of greens and a dash of my 'special' vinaigrette. / 前几天，我在皮埃尔的商店里买了{2}。一堆绿叶蔬菜上加上少许我的“特制”油醋汁真是棒极了。",
        "ProfessorSnail_Hint_828": "My research suggests that a species of frog once lived on this island. They would've inhabited a dark, damp area, with lots of vegetation... / 我的研究表明，这座岛上曾经有一种蛙类，它们很可能栖息在黑暗潮湿且植被丰富的区域……",
        "SummitEvent_Dialogue3_Haley": "*giggle*... $h\"/faceDirection farmer 1 true/emote farmer 8/pause 1000/speak Haley \"Oh, it's just that... / 嘻嘻……$h\"/faceDirection farmer 1 true/emote farmer 8/pause 1000/speak Haley \"啊，是这样的……#$b#As a little girl, I always dreamed that one day, I would climb to the summit with my true love, and share a kiss.$l\" / 我还是个小女孩的时候，就经常会幻想自己有一天会与真爱之人一起爬到山顶，然后接吻。$l\"",
        "ProfessorSnail_Hint_824": "Before I got stuck in that cave, I was exploring the little gully nearby. The stones there are full of fossils! If I were you, I'd be breaking them open to look for bones. / 我被困在洞穴里之前，在探索洞穴附近的一处小溪谷。那里的石头全都是化石！我建议你把它们敲开，在里面找找有没有骨头。",
        "Morris_WeekendGreeting": "Welcome to JojaMart! How is your weekend going? / 欢迎来到 Joja 超市！周末过得怎么样？#$b#We're currently in the process of setting up a brand-new membership system for our customers. Please check back soon to join! / 我们目前正在为客户建立一个全新的会员制。请稍后访问并加入我们！",
        "PurchasedItem_Pierre_QualityLow_Willy": "Ahoy... you know that {2} you sold me the other day? Well, I sizzled it up in me cabin last night... / 你好啊……你还记得那天你卖给我的{2}吗？那啥，我昨晚在自家小屋里把它烧焦了……#$b#T'was the mealiest fish I've ever set me gums on...$s / 那真是我吃过的最干巴巴的鱼了……$s",
        "PurchasedItem_3_QualityLow_Rude": "I went shopping last night and picked up {1} {2} on sale for only {3}g. / 我昨晚去购物了，买了廉价出售的{2}，只需要 {3} 金。#$e# It was {4}! No wonder Pierre was selling that {5} for so cheap... / 那是{4}！难怪皮埃尔的售价{5}那么便宜？",
        "Morris_NoMoreCD": "Ah! My favorite customer... Unfortunately I have no more community development projects available at the moment. / 啊！我最喜欢的顾客……可惜的是，我目前没有更多的社区发展项目了。",
        "Birdie1": "It's rumored that long ago, a great civilization of dwarves lived on this very island. / 传说在很久以前，岛上存在着发达的矮人文明。#$e#Have you been inside the volcano? It's filled with the ruins of their strange machines... / 你去过火山里面吗？到处都是矮人造出的奇怪机器的残骸……",
        "SummitEvent_Dialogue1B_Spouse": "We've been through a lot together, haven't we?$h / 我们一起经历了许多，是不是？$h",
        "Birdie12": "*sigh*... To live in a world of endless potential, we can never know if we've made the right choices.$s / 唉……在这个可能性无限的世界里，我们永远无法知道自己是否做出了正确的选择。$s#$b#Sorry to trouble you, my dear. I sometimes get carried away by thoughts... / 很抱歉打扰到你了，孩子。有时候我会迷失在自己的想法之中……",
        "Birdie_NoGift": "Oh, no no no... I don't need any gifts, my dear. You keep it. / 啊，不不不……我不需要任何礼物，孩子。你留着就好。",
        "JoshHouse_Alex_Trash": "Uh.. What are you doing?$s / 啊……你在做什么？$s",
        "Birdie3": "Have you been to the secret shrine in the jungle? The flowers there smell lovely... It's one of my favorite spots on the island.$h / 你去过雨林里的秘密神庙吗？那里的花闻起来很香……那是我在岛上最喜欢的地方之一。$h",
        "Birdie4": "Every morning for breakfast, I have a bowl of poi and a glass of freshly squeezed mango juice. It keeps me young! / 我每天早上的早餐是一碗芋泥和一杯鲜榨芒果汁。这是我保持年轻的秘诀！",
        "SamHouse_Sam_Trash": "Hey, don't look in there!$a / 嘿，不要看这里！$a",
        "PurchasedItem_5_Foraged": "I bought the tastiest {2} from Pierre's shop the other day. He said he found it himself while exploring the mountains. I didn't know Pierre was such a talented forager! / 前几天，我从皮埃尔的商店买了最美味的{2}。他说，他在探索高山时，发现了它。我没想到皮埃尔是如此能干的采集者！",
        "SummitEvent_Dialogue2_Morris": "But I have to say, this valley has really grown on me, over the years. / 但不可否认，经过这么多年，我越来越喜欢这座山谷。#$b#Working here has opened my eyes to a different way of life. It's hard to say this, but... It's been... a humbling experience. / 在这里的工作经历让我看到了生活的另一面。虽然我很难开口承认，但是……这段经历……能让人学会谦虚。",
        "Birdie0": "I never thought I'd see a new face on this island, dear. But I'm glad you're here! / 孩子，我从来没想过还能在岛上看见新面孔。你能来这里我很高兴！",
        "PurchasedItem_Alex": "Hey, so I picked up {1} {2} at the store last night. Grandma made her special casserole... / 嘿，昨晚，我在商店了买了{2}。奶奶做了顿特别的砂锅菜……",
        "PurchasedItem_Abigail_QualityHigh": "Hey. We had one of those {2}s you sold at the shop for dinner last night... I guess it was starting to go bad and my Dad couldn't bear to throw it out.$h / 嘿。昨晚，我们买了一个你在商店出售的{2}做晚饭……我想它已开始变质了，我的爸爸舍不得扔掉。$h#$b#It was still pretty good, though. / 但是，它仍然是相当不错的。",
        "SummitEvent_Dialogue1_Morris": "You know, when I was first assigned to this location over %year years ago, I considered it a step back in my career. / %year 年前，我刚被指派到这里，当时我觉得自己的事业走了下坡路。#$b#What self-respecting Joja Manager would want to preside over a tiny, backwater location like Pelican Town?$h / 有哪个自尊自爱的 Joja 经理会愿意在鹈鹕镇这样一个狭小而死气沉沉的地方工作呢？$h",
        "SummitEvent_Dialogue3_Emily": "This is a special moment... / 这是个特别的时刻……#$b#I've always known I would be standing here with you, someday. I've always felt it in my heart. / 我一直都知道，我总有一天会和你一起站在这里。我心底一直有着这样的预感。#$b#Now, it's all come true.\"/pause 500/speak Emily \"The world is a mysterious and special place...$l\" / 现在，一切终于成为现实。\"/pause 500/speak Emily \"世界真是神秘又特别……$l\"",
        "PurchasedItem_2_QualityLow_Willy": "Hi... did you sell {1} {2} to the general store the other day? I think I bought it... / 嗨……前些日子你是不是买了{2}给店里？大概是我买下的……#$e#It smelled kind of fishy, but it was alright. / 那鱼闻着有股腥味，不过还凑合。",
        "Mines_PlayerKilled_Linus": "...I found you unconscious in the mines. You're lucky I happened to pass by! / ……我发现你在矿山不省人事。你很幸运，我刚巧路过！#$b#Be a little more careful next time, okay?$s / 下次小心点，好吗？$s",
        "LostItemQuest_DefaultThankYou": "You found it! Thank you. / 你找到了！谢谢。",
        "PurchasedItem_Pierre_QualityHigh": "Hey, remember that {2} you sold me the other day? I ended up serving it to the family for a special dinner. / 嘿，记得前几天你卖给我的{2}吗？我最终把它做成了晚餐。#$b#My wife loved it! ...And Abby even started going to town on it after I smothered the thing in hoisin sauce. $h / 我的妻子喜欢极了！……在我用海鲜沙司煨它时，阿比盖尔竟然开始尽情享用它了。$h#$b#... well,... back to business, huh? / ……好吧……言归正传，哈？",
        "PurchasedItem_Pierre_QualityLow": "Hey, remember that {2} you sold me the other day? I ended up serving it to the family for a special dinner. / 嘿，记得前几天你卖给我的{2}吗？我最终把它做成了晚餐。#$b#I can't say it was a hit... $s / 我不能说晚餐是成功的……$s#$b#... well,... back to business, huh? / ……好吧，……言归正传，哈？",
        "Birdie6": "My hut may be small, but it's more than enough for what I need. And best of all, I built it myself. / 我的屋子可能是小了点，但对我来说已经足够了。它是我造的，就是最好的。"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/mail",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "Lewis": "@,^I'm really glad you've become part of our community! I've enclosed a 500g check from the Stardew Valley Agricultural Fund to help you continue your good work. ^Maybe you can buy some more seeds with it.  ^  Sincerely, Mr. Lewis%item money 500 501 %% / @：^很高兴你能加入我们的社区！我随信给你寄了一张来自星露谷农业基金的 500 金支票，以资助你继续努力工作。^或许你能用它买些种子。^此致敬礼，刘易斯先生 [#]A Gift From Lewis / 来自刘易斯的礼物",
        "LinusCooking": "@,^how are you doing? I've enclosed some instructions on how to make one of my favorite fish recipes. ^   -Linus%item cookingRecipe %% / @：^你最近过的怎么样？我随信附上了我最爱的鱼料理做法。 ^——莱纳斯 [#]Linus' Recipe / 莱纳斯的食谱",
        "dad1": "Dear @,^  Have you settled into your new life yet? I can't believe you're all grown up now... Time sure flies. Now that you're gone I have all this extra money laying around, so I included a little gift.^  Love, Dad.%item money 500 501 %% / 亲爱的@：^你在那里安顿下来了么？真是不敢相信你已经长大成人了啊……时间真是快。现在你在外地，我手头攒了很多钱，所以我还给你寄了一个小礼物。^爱你的爸爸。 [#]From Dad / 爸爸的信",
        "elliottBoat": "Meet me at the docks on a sunny morning. I've got something in mind. ^   -Elliott / 找一天晴朗的清晨到码头来找我。我有些话想和你说。 ^——艾利欧特 [#]Elliott's Note / 艾利欧特的笔记",
        "EmilyCamping": "@,^Let's go camping! ^^ Meet me in the secret woods after 10pm.^^ Love, Emily / @：^我们去野营吧！^^晚上 10 点后我们在秘密森林见。^^爱你，艾米丽 [#]Emily's Invitation / 艾米丽的邀请",
        "WillyTropicalFish": "@,^^Congrats on a successful island fishing trip. I'm proud of ya!^^Here, take this special fish tank. It'll make a great piece in your house.^^-Willy%item id (F)2312 %% / @：^^祝贺你的海岛钓鱼之旅取得成功。为你感到骄傲！^^给，收下这个特制的鱼缸。它会成为你家的一大亮点。^^——威利 [#]Willy's Tropical Challenge / 威利的热带挑战",
        "passedOut1_NotBilled_Male": "Dear Mr. @,^Last night, a Joja team member found you incapacitated. A medical team was dispatched to bring you home safely.^We're glad you're okay!^^Since you have no money, we were obligated by law to provide this service free of charge.^^-Morris^Joja Customer Satisfaction Representative / 亲爱的@先生！^昨晚，Joja 团队的一位员工发现您昏倒了。我们派出了一支医疗小队来把您安全地送回了家里。^很高兴您没有出事！^^由于您没有钱，根据法律我们有义务向您提供免费服务。^^——莫里斯^Joja 顾客满意部门代表 [#]Legally Required Notice / 法律要求的通知",
        "Bouquet": "@,^It seems like you're starting to get close with some of the townspeople. If you want to show someone that you're romantically interested, you've got to give them one of my beautiful flower bouquets. I'm selling them now, for a very fair price! If you want to start a family someday, this is the first step! ^   -Pierre / @：^最近你似乎和镇上的某个人走得很近。如果你想示爱的话，就得送上一束漂亮的鲜花。我这儿卖的花，价钱极其公道！如果你某一天想组建一个家庭，这是第一步！^——皮埃尔 [#]About Bouquets / 关于鲜花",
        "newsstory": "Greetings, @.^It is our pleasure to inform you that your farm will be featured in next week's 'up & coming' column of the Stardew Valley Tribune! Congratulations. We're impressed with your quick progress. ^   -SVT / 您好，@。^很高兴地通知您我们会在星露谷论坛下周的“活力”专栏介绍贵农场！祝贺你！您的显著进步令我们印象深刻。 ^—星露谷论坛 [#]News Story / 新闻故事",
        "Linus": "Hello, friend.^The mountain lake has been kind to me lately. I'd like to share my good fortune with you.  ^   -Linus %item id (O)136 1 (O)143 1 (O)202 1 (O)227 1 (O)228 1 %% / 你好，朋友。^最近我在山湖那里的收获不错。我想和你分享这份好运。 ^——莱纳斯 [#]A Gift From Linus / 一份来自莱纳斯的礼物",
        "winter_24": "Dear @,^Tomorrow is the Feast of the Winter Star.^Did you get a gift for your 'secret friend'... %secretsanta?^The feast starts at 9 AM in the town square. See you then! ^   -Mayor Lewis %% / 亲爱的@：^明天就是冬日星盛宴了！^你有没有为你的“神秘朋友”%secretsanta精心准备一份礼物呢？^宴会在镇里的广场举行，九点开始。不见不散！^——镇长刘易斯 [#]Feast Of The Winter Star Reminder / 冬日星盛宴提醒",
        "robinResource": "Hey @,^^Congratulations on completing my little challenge. I'm impressed!^^As an added bonus, I've included the blueprints for a new type of chest. Enjoy!^^-Robin^^^^P.S. -- Now that you have all those resources laying around, why not swing by for some construction work?%item craftingRecipe Stone_Chest %% / @：^^你好！恭喜你完成了我的小挑战。你太棒了！^^我附上了一种新型箱子的设计图，就当作额外的奖励。希望你喜欢！^^——罗宾^^^^附：既然你已经有这么多资源了，要不要来试试做些建筑工程？ [#]Robin's Resource Rush / 罗宾的资源活动",
        "GusCooking": "Dear @,^Here's a recipe from my saloon. I only share this with my good friends! ^   -Gus%item cookingRecipe %% / 亲爱的 @：^这是我酒吧的食谱。我只和好朋友分享这个！^——格斯 [#]Gus's Recipe / 格斯的配方",
        "winter_13_2": "I've got another challenge for you: Catch me a Lingcod.^They don't go down easy, but I know you can do it.^  -Willy%item quest 124 %% / 我又有一项挑战要来考考你：抓一条蛇齿单线鱼！^这东西不好搞，但我知道你能做到的。^——威利 [#]Willy's Challenge #2 / 威利的挑战#2",
        "spring_2_1": "Hello there,^Just got back from a fishing trip. You should come down to the beach some time.^I've got something for ya.^-Willy %item quest 13 true %% / 你好啊，^我刚刚钓完鱼回来。你偶尔也该来沙滩走走。^我有些东西要给你。^——威利 [#]Willy's Invitation / 威利的邀请",
        "gusGiantOmelet": "Hi @,^^Thanks for the eggs.^The yolks look amazing... I think this will be my best omelet yet!^^Please accept this gift.^^-Gus%item id (BC)216 %% / @：^^你好。感谢你给的蛋。^这蛋黄看起来质量很棒……我觉得这会是我做过的最好的煎蛋卷！^^请收下这份礼物。^^——格斯 [#]Gus' Famous Omelet / 格斯的著名煎蛋卷",
        "quest100": "@,^I am pleased to announce that you've been chosen as \"Neighbor of the year\"! That comes with a 10,000g prize! Congratulations! Everyone in town wants to say 'thanks' for all you've done. ^   -Mayor%item money 10000 10001 %% / @：^我很高兴宣布你当选了\"年度最佳邻居\"！奖金有整整 10,000金哦！衷心地祝贺你！镇上的乡亲们都折服于你的高尚行为！ ^——镇长 [#]Neighbor Of The Year / 年度最佳邻居",
        "QiChallengeComplete": "You did it.^ I'm very impressed.^ Enjoy your reward.^   -Qi. %item money 10000 %% / 你成功了！^我对你真是刮目相看。^这是你的奖励！^——齐先生 [#]Qi Challenge Complete / 齐先生的挑战完成",
        "Duck": "Dear @,^You've proven your ability to raise chickens, so I'm now selling ducks at my shop!       ^   -Marnie / 亲爱的@：^你已经证明了自己养鸡的实力，所以我的店里要开始卖鸭子了！^——玛妮 [#]Ducks For Sale! / 鸭子开始售卖！",
        "afterSamShow": "@,^the show was a rockin' success! I wanted to say thanks again for all your help in creating this amazing band. We couldn't have done it without you!   ^   -Sam / @：^演出取得了巨大成功！我想要再次对你说声谢谢，是你帮我组建了这支不可思议的乐队。没有你，我们成功不了！^——山姆 [#]Sam's Thank-you Note / 山姆的感谢信",
        "passedOut1_Billed_Female": "Dear Ms. @,^Last night, a Joja team member found you incapacitated. A medical team was dispatched to bring you home safely.^We're glad you're okay!^^(You've been billed {0}g for this service)^^-Morris^Joja Customer Satisfaction Representative / 亲爱的@小姐！^昨晚，Joja 团队的一位员工发现您昏倒了。我们派出了一支医疗小队来把您安全地送回了家里。^很高兴您没有出事！^^（这个服务会向您收取 {0} 金的费用）^^——莫里斯^Joja 顾客满意部门代表 [#]Joja Invoice / Joja 的账单",
        "robinWell": "Robin here!^I know there's a lot of stone scattered around your farm.^If you have a surplus, you might consider having me build a well for you.^Wells can be placed all over your farm, and serve as convenient places to refill your watering can.^^Just swing by my shop with 75 stones and 1000g when you're ready for it.^-Robin / 我是罗宾！^我了解到你的农场周围有很多散落的碎石。^如果碎石有富余的话，你或许可以考虑让我给你建口井。^井可以建在农场里的任何地方，这样你给喷壶打水就更方便了。^^等你准备好了，带上 75 个石头和 1,000 金来我店里就行。^——罗宾 [#]Build A Well / 建一口井",
        "FizzIntro": "Hello.^^I've heard you're working on a very special challenge.^^I have the 'perfect' solution to help you out.^^Meet me in the watery cave on Ginger Island.^^-Fizz^Joja Special Services Division / 你好。^^我听说你在挑战一个很特殊的目标。^^我这里有一个能“完美”帮到你的解决方案。^^我在姜岛上有水的洞穴里等你。^^——菲兹^Joja 特别服务部门 [#]Letter From Fizz / 菲兹的信",
        "WoodChipper": "Hey @,^^Just wanted to let you know about a new item I'm carrying... it's called a 'Wood Chipper'.^^You can use it to break hardwood into several pieces of regular wood!^^I know wood can be hard to come by in the winter, so if your supply gets low, consider picking one up.^       -Robin / 你好，@：^^我想告诉你我们进了一个新东西……它叫做“碎木机”。^^你可以用它把硬木削成几块普通木头！^^我知道冬天很难找到木材，所以如果木材不太够了，可以考虑买一个。^       ——罗宾 [#]Wood Chipper Notice / 碎木机提示",
        "Shane": "Hey,^I thought it would be fun to send you a letter. I don't really know what to write, though.^ Here, I've enclosed a treat for you. Don't tell anyone, but I snagged this from the back room of JojaMart ages ago.^Okay, see you soon. ^   -Shane %item id (O)215 1 (O)206 1 %% / 嘿，^我觉得给你写信会很有趣。虽然我其实不怎么会写。^我随信附上了一个小礼物。别告诉其他人，这是很久以前我从 Joja 超市里搞来的。^好了，回头见。 ^——谢恩 [#]A Gift From Shane / 来自谢恩的礼物",
        "KrobusCrafting": "@, I'm not sure how the human message system works, so I asked Wizard to help me write this letter.^^I hope you are doing okay.^^I wanted to share this with you... it's notes on how my people build a certain item.^^   -Krobus%item craftingRecipe Dark_Sign %% / @，我不知道人类的信是怎么写的，所以我请法师帮我写了这封信。^^希望你一切都好。^^我想给你看看这个……是我的同族人制作一样东西的笔记……^^——科罗布斯 [#]A letter from Krobus / 来自科罗布斯的信",
        "PamCooking": "Hey Kid,^here's the recipe for a little treat my pappy used to make. Cook it slow. ^   -Pam%item cookingRecipe %% / 孩子你好，^这是我老爸常做的一道小菜的配方。要小火慢炖才行。 ^——潘姆 [#]Pam's Recipe / 潘姆的配方",
        "spring_1_2": "Notice:^^The price of raw materials at Robin's shop and Clint's shop has increased. / 通知：^^罗宾商店和克林特商店的原材料价格已经上涨。 [#]Raw Material Price Notice / 原材料涨价通知",
        "CF_Fish": "Dear @,^ Your angling skills surpass even my ol' Pappy's... I'm impressed. ^ This stardrop's been passed down from Willy Sr. to Willy Jr. for... oh, heck. Prob'ly a thousand years.^Seein' as I don't have any kids... I want you to have it.^^ -Willy   ^  %item id (O)434 1 %% / 亲爱的@：^你的钓鱼技术比我家老头子还厉害啊！我很震撼。^这个星之果实从老威利传到小威利，再传到……哇。反正有快一千年的历史了。^我膝下无子……干脆把他传给你吧。^^——威利 ^ [#]Willy's Family Heirloom / 威利的传家宝",
        "Emily": "Hi!^How are you doing? I hope you enjoy the gift I've sent you... Well, goodbye! +   ^   -Emily %item id (O)397 1 (O)428 1 (O)440 1 %% / 嗨！^你还好吗？希望你能喜欢我给你送去的礼物……那么，再见！^——艾米丽 [#]A Gift From Emily / 来自艾米丽的礼物",
        "afterArtShow": "Dear @,^Thanks again for coming to my art show. It was such a success! I sold nearly all of my sculptures, and everyone was so positive and encouraging! I hope to see you again soon.  ^   -Leah / 亲爱的@：^多谢光临我的艺术展！简直太成功了！我几乎把雕像都卖完了，而大家的肯定是对我巨大的鼓舞！希望很快就能见到你。 ^——莉亚 [#]Leah's Thank-you Note / 莉亚的感谢信",
        "ClintReward2": "Um, Hello...     ^Thanks for helping me clear out more monsters.^^Maybe next time, I'll take care of them myself... if I have time!^^Take this item. I found it in the back room...^^   -Clint, the blacksmith%item id (O)286 10 (O)287 5 (O)231 3 %% / 呃，你好……^谢谢你帮我清掉了更多怪物。^^也许下次我就能自己收拾它们了……如果我有空！^^给你这个，是我在里屋找到的……^^——铁匠克林特 [#]Clint's Alternate Thank-you / 克林特的再次感谢",
        "fertilizers2": "Dear @,^I am now selling higher quality fertilizers, as well as new crop selections! See you soon. ^   -Pierre / 亲爱的@：^现在店里进了一批高品质的化肥和新的谷物种子！欢迎光临！ ^——皮埃尔 [#]Pierre's High Quality Fertilizers / 皮埃尔的高品质肥料",
        "linusTrashCleanup": "Hi @,^^Thanks for helping me clean up around the valley.^The waters are looking much cleaner. I think everyone will appreciate it. I know I will.^As a way of saying 'thanks', I wanted to teach you how to grow your own fiber. I hope it's useful.^^-Linus%item craftingRecipe Fiber_Seeds %% / @：^^你好。谢谢你帮忙清理山谷。^水看起来清澈多了。谢谢你，而且我想大家都会感谢你的。^为了表达“感谢”，我想教你种植纤维的方法。希望能帮到你。^^——莱纳斯 [#]Linus' Thank You / 莱纳斯的感谢",
        "Caroline": "Dear @,^Here's a vegetable from the little garden I keep out back. You probably have more veggies than you know what to do with, but oh well.   ^   -Caroline%item id (O)190 1 (O)192 1 (O)24 1 %% / 亲爱的@：^这是我在小院里种的青菜。或许你那儿的蔬菜已经多到连你都不知该怎么处理了，但没关系。 ^—卡洛琳 [#]A Gift From Caroline / 来自卡洛琳的礼物",
        "mom3": "Dear @,^  I saw an article about you in the local paper! It sounds like the country life is a good fit for you! I'm so proud of you. Take care, sweety. Love, Mom / 亲爱的@：^我在报纸上看到关于你的报道了！乡村生活看起来很合你胃口呢！我真的为你感到自豪。好好照顾你自己，我的小甜心。爱你的妈妈。 [#]From Mom #3 / 妈妈的信 #3",
        "hatter": "Hi.^^Me sell hats. Okay, poke?^^Come to old old old haus, poke. Bring coines.^^-hat mouse / 嗨。^^窝卖帽子。听懂了吗，波克？^^波克，到破房兹这里来。带点金闭。^^——帽子老鼠 [#]Hiyo, Poke / 嗨哟，波克",
        "passedOut3_NotBilled": "@,^Someone dropped you off at the clinic last night. You'd passed out from exhaustion!^You've got to take better care of yourself and go to bed at a reasonable hour.^Since you have no money, I provided your medical care free of charge.^^-Dr. Harvey / @：^昨晚有人将你送到诊所了。你因中暑而晕倒！^你要照顾好自己，并在合适的时间及时睡觉。^由于你没有钱，我想你提供免费的医疗服务。^^——哈维医生 [#]Harvey's Free Medical Service / 哈维免费的医疗服务",
        "landslideDone": "To our valued JojaMart customers:^Our team members have removed the landslide caused by our drilling operation near the mountain lake. I'd like to remind you that our drilling operation is entirely legal (pursuant to init. L61091, JojaCo Amendment). Responsible stewardship of the local environment is our top priority! ^^We apologize for any inconvenience this accident may have caused.^As always, we value your continued support and patronage!^^-Morris,^Joja Customer Satisfaction Representative / 尊敬的 Joja 超市的顾客：^我们的团队成员已经清理了山体滑坡现场，这次山体滑坡是受到我们公司钻井活动的影响。我们必须声明我们的钻井活动是完全合法的（依据 Joja 公司第 L61091 修正案）而保护当地环境一直都是我们的优先考量！^^我们对这次的意外带来的不便深感歉意。^我们由衷地对顾客的支持和赞助表示感谢！^^——莫里斯^Joja 顾客满意部门代表 [#]Joja Removed Landslide / Joja 清理滑坡",
        "skullCave": "I see you've entered the Skull Cavern. Well done.^I've got a better challenge for you, kid. Make it at least 25 levels deep. I've got a mountain of $ to send if you can do it.^  Your friend, Mr. Qi %item quest 20 %% / 我看到你之前曾进入到头骨山洞里。干得好。^年轻人，我有一个更大的挑战要交给你。等你达到至少25层的时候才算是完成任务。如果你能完成任务的话，我会给你一座山的 $ 。^你的朋友，齐先生 [#]Qi's Challenge / 齐先生的挑战",
        "DesertFestival": "Dear @,^^Tomorrow begins a 3-day festival in Calico Desert.^^With the bus back in order, we're all delighted to be able to continue this time-honored, beloved tradition.^^There will be games, free food, prizes, and much more!^^Also, two townspeople are selected each day to run a little shop, so make sure you swing by and check out what they have to offer.^^See you there!^-Lewis / 亲爱的@：^^明天开始会在卡利科沙漠庆祝节日，为期 3 天。^^多亏巴士修好了，我们得以延续这个历史悠久的传统，大家都十分高兴。^^到时候会有趣味游戏、免费食物、丰厚奖品，活动多多！^^另外，每天会有两位镇上的居民负责开小商店，记得来逛逛，看看有什么可以买的。^^期待在节日上见到你！^——刘易斯 [#]Desert Festival Reminder / 沙漠节提醒",
        "Pigs": "Dear @,^You've come a long way since you first arrived. As a result, I've decided to start selling pigs at my shop. These pigs are trained at finding gourmet truffles!       ^   -Marnie / 亲爱的@：^从你刚来时算起，已经取得很多成果。所以，我决定在店里卖猪。这些猪都受过训练，能找到美味的松露！^——玛妮 [#]Pigs For Sale! / 猪开始售卖！",
        "foundLostTools": "Dear @,^Someone dropped your tools into the lost and found bin last night.^^Stop by the mayor's office to pick them up. ^^  -Mayor Lewis / 亲爱的@：^昨晚有人找到你的工具，放进失物招领箱了。^^到镇长办公室来拿吧。^^——镇长刘易斯 [#]Lost Tools / 丢失的工具",
        "summer_28": "Dear @,^Tonight at around 10 o'clock PM, a rare and beautiful event will take place.^^The moonlight jellies will be passing by Pelican Town on their long journey south for the winter.^^We're all gathering at the beach to watch. You don't want to miss this!^See you tonight,^ -Demetrius / 亲爱的@：^今晚大约 10 点钟，会举行一项极其罕见但绚丽的盛事。^^月光水母在他们冬天往南迁徙的旅途上会经过鹈鹕镇！^^我们都会聚在沙滩上一起观赏。可不要错过哦！^今晚见，^——德米特里厄斯 [#]Dance Of The Moonlight Jellies / 月光水母之舞",
        "RobinCooking": "Dear @,^here is an old recipe that my grandma passed down to me. Enjoy!   ^   -Robin%item cookingRecipe %% / 亲爱的@：^这是我奶奶传授给我的古老配方。祝您生活愉快！^——罗宾 [#]Robin's Family Recipe / 罗宾的祖传配方",
        "winter_7": "Dear @,^Tomorrow we're all gathering in front of Marnie's house for the Festival of Ice.^^It's a celebration of winter... there'll be snowmen, ice sculptures, and an ice fishing competition!^Arrive between 9 AM and 2 PM if you'd like to participate.^  -Mayor Lewis / 亲爱的@：^明天我们会在玛妮家前集合，庆祝冰雪节。^^这是我们欢庆冬天的日子……我们会堆雪人、做冰雕，还会有钓鱼比赛呢！^如果你感兴趣，早上 9 点到下午 2 点左右来和我们一起庆祝吧。^——镇长刘易斯 [#]Festival Of Ice Notice / 冰雪节通知",
        "spring_19_1": "Farmer @-^I have a request for you. I need fresh cauliflower for a recipe I want to make. Could you bring me one?^   -Jodi%item quest 101 %% / 农夫  @：^你可以帮帮我么，我需要花椰菜做一道菜，你可以给我点么？^——乔迪 [#]Jodi Asks For Cauliflower / 乔迪需要花椰菜",
        "Robin": "Hey there!^I had some extra wood lying around... I thought maybe you could use it. Take care!  ^   -Robin %item id (O)388 50 %% / 嘿，你好！^我这儿还有些剩余的木头……你或许用得着。请多多保重！^——罗宾 [#]A Gift From Robin / 来自罗宾的礼物",
        "marnieAutoGrabber": "@,^I've got a new item in stock... It's called the \"Auto-Grabber\".^^This thing can milk your cows and goats, shear your sheep, gather eggs, and pluck your wooly rabbits... all on its own!^^It's considered a 'luxury item', so I'm charging 25,000g.^^    -Marnie / @：^我的存货中新添了一件东西……叫做“自动采集器”。^^这件东西可以给奶牛和山羊挤奶、给绵羊剪羊毛、拾取鸡蛋和鸭毛……一切全自动！^^堪称是“奢侈品”，所以我开价 25000 金。^^——玛妮 [#]Auto-Grabber Notice / 自动采集器通知",
        "Sheep": "Dear @,^You've proven your ability to raise cows, so I'm now selling sheep at my shop!       ^   -Marnie / 亲爱的@：^你已经证明了自己养牛的实力，所以我的店里要开始卖山羊了！^——玛妮 [#]Sheep For Sale! / 绵羊开始售卖！",
        "fall_6_2": "Wanted: 1 Fresh Lobster for a marvelous bisque I'm creating.^Who: Gus, proprietor of the Stardrop Saloon^Reward: 800g %item quest 121 %% / 征集：我需要一只新鲜的龙虾来制作美妙的浓汤。^征集人：星果酒吧的老板格斯^奖励：800 金 [#]Gus Needs Lobster / 格斯需要龙虾",
        "carolineSO": "Hi @,^^Lewis told me that you've been shipping a lot of ingredients from the island! It's great to have access to new produce... it really opens a whole new world of culinary possibilities!^I'm including a gift for you... some blueprints you might find useful.^^-Caroline%item craftingRecipe Solar_Panel %% / @：^^你好。刘易斯告诉我你从岛上运了很多食材过来！有机会接触新的材料真是太好了……这样我就能继续在烹饪上大显身手了！^我给你准备了一份礼物……是你可能用得上的设计图。^^——卡洛琳 [#]Caroline's Tropical Ingredients / 卡洛琳的热带食材",
        "GeorgeCooking": "Figured I'd give you this recipe I had laying around. Try not to burn it. ^   -George%item cookingRecipe %% / 这份配方我留着也没用，索性给你试试吧。小心别把它烧了。 ^——乔治 [#]George's Recipe / 乔治的食谱",
        "summer_15_2": "Dear Farmer @,^I'd like to give my wife a starfruit for our anniversary. Are you growing any on your farm? If you brought me one, I'd be very grateful.^   -Kent%item quest 119 %% / 亲爱的农夫@：^我想在结婚纪念日的时候送给妻子一颗杨桃。你在农场里种杨桃了吗？如果你能给我带一个的话，我会很感激你的。^——肯特 [#]Kent Needs A Gift / 肯特需要一个礼物",
        "Evelyn": "Hello there, dear,  I hope your farm is doing well.^ I'm sending you a little something from my kitchen... I hope it didn't crumble in the mail.  ^   -Evelyn  %item id (O)216 1 (O)220 1 (O)223 1 %% / 你好，亲爱的，希望你的农场一切都好。^我在厨房里做了点儿东西，给你寄去……但愿别在信里压碎了。 ^——艾芙琳 [#]A Gift From Evelyn / 来自艾芙琳的礼物",
        "winter_12_1": "@-^I am researching the forgotten art of shadow divination. I require an item known as 'Void Essence'. Bring it to me and you will be rewarded.^ -M. Rasmodius, Wizard %item quest 111 %% / @：^我现在正在研究影子占卜这项失传的法术。我需要“虚空精华”进行我的研究。帮我找到它我会给你报酬的。^——法师 M·拉斯莫迪斯 [#]Wizard's Request / 法师的请求",
        "fall_15": "Dear @,^I just want to remind you that the Stardew Valley Fair is happening tomorrow.^Don't forget to bring your 9 items for the grange display.^Remember, the fair starts at 9AM in the town square. See you there!^   -Mayor Lewis / 亲爱的@：^我想你一定知道明天就是星露谷展览会了吧。^记得带上九件物品来参加农庄展览。^注意，博览会会在明天上午 9 点在镇上广场举行。期待你的参与！^——镇长刘易斯 [#]Stardew Valley Fair Reminder / 星露谷展会提醒",
        "Kent": "Hello, @.^This item was collecting dust in the tool shed. I figured you might be able to use it.  ^   -Kent%item id (O)286 1 (O)287 1 (O)288 1 (O)787 1 %% / 你好，@。^这东西一直放在工具房里积灰。我想你也许用得上它。 ^——肯特 [#]A Gift From Kent / 来自肯特的礼物",
        "haleyGarden": "@,^I thought it would be fun to write you a note.^ I had so much fun with the cows yesterday... I'm starting to understand why you chose the farmer's life! Hope to see you soon.  ^   -Haley / @：^我觉得给你写封短信会很有趣。^昨天我和奶牛玩儿得很尽兴……我开始理解你为什么会选择田园生活了！希望很快就能见到你。 ^——海莉 [#]Haley's Note / 海莉的短信",
        "passedOutIsland_Leo": "Hi @,^^Last night, I found you slumbering in the dark.^It wasn't a very safe place, so the bird friends air-lifted you to your bed.^Please be careful from now on.^^-Leo^^P.S. Willy helped me write this. / @：^^你好。昨晚我发现你在暗处睡着了。^那个地方不太安全，所以鸟儿朋友们把你空运到了床上。^之后还请多注意安全。^^——雷欧^^备注：信是威利帮我写的。",
        "LeoCooking": "@,^Here's a food from my home, that me and my family enjoy. Hope you like it. ^^  -Leo^^P.S. Willy helped me write this.%item cookingRecipe %% / @：^这是我家乡的一种食物，大伙都很爱吃，希望你也喜欢。^^——雷欧^^备注：信是威利帮我写的。 [#]Leo's Recipe / 雷欧的食谱",
        "guildQuest": "I see you've been exploring the old mine. You've got the adventurer's spirit, that much I can tell.^If you can slay 10 slimes, you'll have earned your place in my adventurer's guild. ^Be careful.    -Marlon %item quest 15 true %% / 我发现你一直在探索那个旧矿井。我只能说，你生来就是个探险者。^只要击杀 10 只史莱姆， 你就能在我的探险家公会里拥有一席之地。^小心点。——马龙 [#]Quest To Slay Slimes / 史莱姆击杀任务",
        "Pam": "Hey. ^I found this in a drawer somewhere. Thought you could use it.   ^   -Pam %item id (O)346 1 (O)349 1 (O)787 1 %% / 嘿。^我在抽屉里找到了这个。我想你可能用得着。 ^——潘姆 [#]A Gift From Pam / 来自潘姆的礼物",
        "Clint": "Um, Hello...     ^Sorry, I'm not good at writing letters. I made one metal bar too many, and I thought you might need it.  ^   -Clint, the blacksmith %item id (O)334 1 (O)335 1 (O)336 1 %% / 呃，你好……^抱歉，我不怎么会写信。我一不小心做多了金属棒，或许你能用得上。^—铁匠克林特 [#]A Gift From Clint / 来自克林特的礼物",
        "spring_11_1": "MISSING:^I lost my favorite Axe! If you find it, please return ASAP. I'm having a tough time without it. There's 250g in it for whoever finds the thing.^   -Robin%item quest 100 %% / 寻物启事：^我把我的爱斧丢了！有谁捡到的话请即刻归还。没有它我非常不方便！任何找到它的人都能得到 250 金的奖励。^——罗宾 [#]Robin Lost Her Axe / 罗宾弄丢了斧子",
        "winter_5_2": "@,^I'm creating an enchanted staff of phenomenal power.^However, I'm missing something: an Iridium Bar.^I'm willing to pay 5x the market value for it. Bring it as soon as you can.^ -M. Rasmodius, Wizard %item quest 123 %% / @：^我在制作一支蕴藏有惊人力量的法杖。^但是,我现在需要一个铱锭！^我愿意出 5 倍的市价买它。快点帮我搞到。^——法师 M·拉斯莫迪斯 [#]Wizard Needs A Rare Item / 法师需要稀有物品",
        "mom4": "Dear @,^ How are things going? You must really be making a fortune on that farm. Don't forget your dear old mother when you're a millionaire! ^  Love, Mom   ^   P.S. Enjoy the cake!%item id (O)221 1 %% / 亲爱的@：^最近过的怎么样啊？你一定在农场那边赚了很多钱吧！就算变成百万富翁也别忘记你的老妈哦！^爱你的妈妈。 ^附：好好享用蛋糕吧！ [#]From Mom #4 / 妈妈的信 #4",
        "Marnie": "Dear @,^You're such a good neighbor I thought I'd send over some animal feed to make your job easier. Keep it up! ^   -Marnie %item id (O)178 30 %% / 亲爱的@：^你是个好邻居，所以我想送些动物饲料给你，或许能帮得上你的忙。继续努力吧！^——玛妮 [#]A Gift From Marnie / 来自玛妮的礼物",
        "stardewHeroMine": "Secret Message: If you can reach the bottom of the mines one more time, a secret awaits you. Be careful, the mines have become more dangerous. / 秘密信息:如果你能再一次下到矿井底部的话，你会发现有一个秘密在等着你发掘。但是小心点，现在矿井越来越危险了。 [#]Secret Message / 秘密信息",
        "WizardReward2": "Thanks to the ectoplasm you delivered to me, I've made a major breakthrough in the field of arcane engineering.^^Enclosed, you'll find blueprints for a most useful machine...^^   -M. Rasmodius, Wizard%item craftingRecipe Mini-Obelisk %% / 多亏你送来的灵外质，我的奥术有了重要突破。^^随信附上一张非常实用的机器的设计图……^^——法师 M·拉斯莫迪斯 [#]The Wizard's Breakthrough / 法师的突破",
        "MarnieCooking": "Dear neighbor,^When I'm not taking care of animals I like to experiment in the kitchen. Since we've become friends I want to share some recipes with you.^I hope you like this! ^   -Marnie%item cookingRecipe %% / 亲爱的邻居，^在照料动物之余，我喜欢在厨房里做些新尝试。既然我们成为了朋友，我想和你分享一些我的配方。^希望你能喜欢！^——玛妮 [#]Marnie's Recipe / 玛妮的配方",
        "passedOut4": "@, ^^Found you face-down in the mud during my 3:00 AM sweep.^^You should try to make it home a little earlier next time!^^     -Marlon / @：^^我在凌晨三点清扫的时候发现你趴在泥地里。^^下次你应该尽可能早一点回家！^^     ——马龙 [#]Note From Marlon / 马龙的便条",
        "robinKitchenLetter": "Dear Farmer @,^^I'd like to apologize for joking about your Grandpa's old cottage when we first met. It's really a nice little house!^^However, you might need some more space someday. That's where I can help. If you bring me some raw materials and pay a fee, I can expand your house.^(Continued on next page)^^The first expansion I offer includes a kitchen. With a kitchen, you'll be able to cook any recipes you've learned!^^Anyway, I hope you're starting to feel at home in Stardew Valley!^^    Your local carpenter,^        Robin / 亲爱的农夫@：^^我们第一次见面的时候我嘲笑了你爷爷的老木屋，我现在想向你道歉。它其实是一间很不错的屋子！^^然而，也许有一天你会需要扩展出更多的空间。那时我就能帮上忙了。^如果你能带给我一些原材料，并且支付一定的费用的话，我就能帮你扩建你的房子。^^我首先计划帮你扩建出一间厨房。有了厨房，你就可以在那里捣鼓你新学习的菜单了！^^总之，我希望你把星露谷当成自己的家乡！^^星露谷的木匠^罗宾 [#]Robin's Services / 罗宾的服务",
        "CarolineTea": "Dear @,^^Thanks for stopping by my sunroom yesterday. I usually drink tea alone, but it was fun to share with you!^^I've enclosed instructions on how to prepare and grow your own tea. No pressure, but if you do end up growing some, make sure to bring me a cup!^^-Caroline%item craftingRecipe Tea_Sapling %% / 亲爱的@：^^感谢你昨天来我的日光房做客。我经常独自喝茶，但和你一起享用真的很愉快！^^我随信附上了自己种植茶叶的前期准备和具体步骤。不要有压力，不过如果你最后种植成功了，请一定要给我带一杯你的茶！^^——卡洛琳 [#]Caroline's Tea Note / 卡洛琳的种茶笔记",
        "quest35": "Dear @,^You've been such a help around town since you moved here... everyone keeps telling me all the wonderful things you've done for them! Please accept this thank-you prize. ^   -Mayor%item money 2500 2501 %% / 亲爱的@：^你搬来镇上之后，一直都很乐于助人……大家都一直向我夸赞你！请收下这份谢礼。^——镇长 [#]Thank-you From Lewis / 刘易斯的谢礼",
        "elliottLetter2": "My dear @,^^The first reading went well, though the audience was a bit smaller than I'd hoped. Still, I sold enough copies of the book to pay for my (bug-infested) hotel room!^^In a few hours, I leave for Zuzu City. If yesterday's reading was a warm-up, this next one will be a true napalm blast...^^I miss you very much. Remember to eat well! Oh, and don't forget the leftover crab cakes I put in the fridge...^-Love, Elliott %item conversationTopic ElliottGone3 0 %% / 亲爱的@：^^我的第一次阅读会还不错，尽管观众比我期望的要少一些。不过，我还是卖了挺多的书，足够支付我的旅馆房间费用！（虽然虫子很多）^^过几个小时，我就要动身前往祖祖城。如果把昨天的阅读会比作热身运动的话，接下来这一场就像真枪实弹了……^^我很想你。记住要好好吃饭！哦，还有，别忘了我剩了些蟹黄糕在冰箱里……^——爱你的，艾利欧特 [#]Letter From My Husband 2 / 我丈夫的信 2",
        "fall_8_1": "Hello,^It's blackberry season right now. The bushes are full of them. I want to pick some, but I lost my basket. Can you help?^   -Linus%item quest 107 %% / 你好，^又到了黑莓成熟的季节。外面的草丛里都是黑莓，我想摘点回去，但是我找不到我的篮子了。你可以帮我吗？^——莱纳斯 [#]Linus Lost His Basket / 莱纳斯弄丢了篮子",
        "fertilizers": "Dear neighbor,^I hope you are feeling settled in your new home. I am writing to let you know that Pierre's store is now selling fertilizers! Why don't you swing by and see if you can afford a few dozen boxes or so?  ^   -Pierre / 亲爱的邻居，^希望你已经安顿好自己的新家了。我写信是想告诉你皮埃尔，的杂货店进了一批肥料！要不要去杂货店那里看看有什么要买的呢？ ^——皮埃尔 [#]Pierre's Fertilizers / 皮埃尔的肥料",
        "passedOut2": "@, ^You're lucky I found you last night! You were unconscious, and someone was searching your pockets. I have no idea how much money they took... they ran away as soon as I approached. Be more careful!^^-Linus / @：^你真幸运，我昨晚找到你了！你都没有意识了，而且有人在翻你的口袋。我不知道他们拿走了你多少钱……我接近你的时候他们迅速跑走了。要多加小心啊！^^——莱纳斯 [#]Note From Linus / 莱纳斯的笔记",
        "winter_18": "Dear @,^I would like to give you some information about an upcoming event: the Feast of the Winter Star. It's a time for the community to come together and think back on all the good fortune we've had this year.^A favorite tradition is the \"secret gift exchange\", where everyone in town is randomly assigned to someone else. On the day of the festival, everyone brings a gift for their secret friend and surprises them with something special!^This year, your secret friend is:^    %secretsanta ^Don't tell anyone! The feast will take place on the 25th from 9AM to 2PM at the town square. See you then! ^   -Mayor Lewis %% / 亲爱的@：^我想和你说下最近的节日和盛事：冬日星盛宴。在这个节日里我们欢聚在一起，回忆过去的一年我们的劳动成果。^我们有一项好玩的传统 \"秘密礼物交换\"，每个人都会随机分配到一位朋友。在宴会的那天，大家都会拿出精心准备的礼物让你的朋友大吃一惊！^今年，你的“神秘朋友”是:^^别告诉任何人哦！宴会在 25 号的 9 点到 2 点，在镇上的广场举行。不见不散！^——镇长刘易斯 [#]Secret Gift-Giver / 秘密的送礼人",
        "ShaneCooking": "@,^I found this recipe in a magazine and I thought it sounded interesting. Feel free to give me a taste if you make it. hehe. ^   -Shane%item cookingRecipe %% / @：^我在杂志上看到了这个配方，看起来挺有意思的。如果你照着做了，不妨让我尝尝吧。 ^——谢恩 [#]Shane's Recipe / 谢恩的配方",
        "abbySpiritBoard": "Hi @.^One of these days you should come to my room after dark... Maybe around 8pm. ^I want to show you something. ^   -Abby / 嗨@。^这几天晚上你可以抽空来我家坐坐……大概晚上八点吧。^我有样东西要给你看。 ^——阿比盖尔 [#]Abby's Note / 阿比盖尔的笔记",
        "DemetriusReward": "Hi @,^^Thanks for your help with the fish.^Nature is usually good at keeping things balanced, but sometimes artificial factors can cause an imbalance.^^I've enclosed a blueprint from a science magazine that you might find interesting.^^-Demetrius%item craftingRecipe Farm_Computer %% / @：^^你好！感谢你帮我处理了鱼的问题。^大自然通常自己会保持平衡，但有时人为因素会破坏生态平衡。^^随信附上来自科学杂志的一份设计图，你可能会感兴趣。^^——德米特里厄斯 [#]Demetrius' Thank You / 德米特里厄斯的感谢",
        "winter_21_1": "@-^How are you doing? Hope the winter hasn't been too hard on you.^Anyway, I'm writing to ask you for some hardwood. I need about ten pieces, if you've got it.^If not, no worries. Take Care!^  -Robin%item quest 113 %% / @：^你还好吗？这个冬天不会太难熬吧？^总之，我想问问你有没有硬木。有的话给我十块。^没有的话就算了。保重！^——罗宾 [#]Robin's Request / 罗宾的请求",
        "Jodi": "Dear @,^I ordered too much fertilizer for the garden!! I bet you can put it to some good use. Take care!  ^   -Jodi %item id (O)368 5 (O)369 5 (O)370 5 %% / 亲爱的@：^我给花园订购了太多肥料了！！我想你应该用得上。请多多保重！^——乔迪 [#]A Gift From Jodi / 来自乔迪的礼物",
        "ClintReward": "Um, Hello...     ^Thanks for helping me clear out those monsters.^^I'm not scared at all! ...But it should make the mines safer for everyone else... right?^^Take this blueprint. (Hope it doesn't make me obsolete...)^^   -Clint, the blacksmith%item craftingRecipe Geode_Crusher %% / 呃，你好……^谢谢你帮我清掉了那些怪物。^^我一点也不害怕的！……但是维护矿井的安全是有必要的，对大家都好……是不是？^^给你这个设计图。（有了这个也别忘了光顾我的铺子啊……）^^——铁匠克林特 [#]Clint's Thank-you / 克林特的感谢",
        "summer_21_2": "@,^I need truffle oil. Don't ask me why.^ -Mayor Lewis%item quest 120 %% / @：^我需要松露油。别问原因。^——镇长刘易斯 [#]Lewis' Request / 刘易斯的请求",
        "fall_19_1": "@-^I'd like to buy a pumpkin from you. My daughter and I want to carve a jack-o-lantern for the upcoming Spirit's Eve festival. ^   -Caroline%item quest 108 %% / @：^我想买个南瓜。我和女儿想在万灵节刻一个南瓜灯。 ^—卡洛琳 [#]Caroline's Request / 卡洛琳的请求",
        "Wizard": "Greetings, young adept.^I have enclosed in this package an item of arcane significance. Use it wisely.   ^   -M. Rasmodius, Wizard%item id (O)422 1 (O)82 1 (O)84 1 (O)70 1 %% / 你好，年轻的术士。^我在包裹里装了一只神器。请谨慎使用。 ^——法师 M·拉斯莫迪斯 [#]A Gift From the Wizard / 来自法师的礼物",
        "PennyCleanTrailer": "Sorry about what happened at my place yesterday... My mom can get into bad moods sometimes.^Please just forget it happened.  ^   -Penny / 我要为昨天发生在我家的事情道歉……我妈偶尔会心情不好。^请把不快都忘掉吧。 ^——潘妮 [#]Penny's Apology / 潘妮的道歉",
        "fall_19_2": "NOTICE^Does anybody have one of them battery packs? My TV remote died, and it's a real hassle getting off the couch to change the station.^  -Pam%item quest 122 %% / 通知^有谁有电池吗？我电视遥控器没电了，我实在懒得从椅子上下来去换台了。^——潘姆 [#]Pam Needs Help / 潘姆需要帮助",
        "fall_9": "Dear @,^One week from today, we are holding the Stardew Valley Fair in the town square!^It's the biggest event of the year, drawing people from all across the country to our humble town.^If you'd like, you can set up a grange display for the event. Just bring up to 9 items that best showcase your talents. You'll be judged on the quality and diversity of your display.^The fair starts at 9 AM... don't miss it!^   -Mayor Lewis / 亲爱的@：^我们将在一周后的今天举办星露谷展览会！^这项年度盛事会吸引全国各地的人们来到我们这个平和的小镇！^如果你想参加的话，你可以进行农庄展览。你只需要带上最能展示你才华的九份展览品。将对你的展品质量和品种进行评价！^展览会会在上午 9 点开始，别错过哦！^——镇长刘易斯 [#]Stardew Valley Fair Notice / 星露谷展会通知",
        "summer_10": "Dear @,^Tomorrow we're all gathering at the beach for the annual Pelican Town Luau.^^The highlight of the event is the communal potluck. Make sure you bring something good to contribute!^The governor himself is attending the event, so make sure you're on your best behavior.^Come to the beach sometime between 9 AM and 2 PM.^   -Mayor Lewis / 亲爱的@：^明天我们会聚集在沙滩上，庆祝一年一度的鹈鹕镇宴会。^^这个盛宴的高潮就在于共享百乐餐。记得把好吃的贡献出来哦！^州长也会亲临现场，请注意自己的言行。^请在上午 9 点到下午 2 点之间到沙滩出席宴会^——镇长刘易斯 [#]Luau Notice / 宴会通知",
        "elliottLetter5": "My dear @,^^I won't bore you with any more details about my readings. They are mostly the same.^^I'm sure your time has been much more exciting! I can't wait to return and see what progress has been made.^^On these long travels between towns, I amuse myself by closing my eyes and envisioning the farm... I see kegs pulsing with sweet wine, a furnace ablaze with precious ore, and our little kitchen with the smell of cinnamon and nutmeg. There's a lot to enjoy!^^Just don't stay out too late in the mines, my love. It's dangerous in there! If you must go... bring plenty of food.^^-Love, Elliott %item conversationTopic ElliottGone6 0 %% / 亲爱的@：^^我不会再写阅读会的细节让你感到无聊了。它们基本都差不多。^^我相信你的经历一定更令人兴奋！我迫不及待地想回来看看都发生了什么。^^在城镇之间的长途旅行中，我闭上眼睛，想象着农场，让自己更开心……我看见酒桶里摆着甜酒，炉子里燃烧着珍贵的矿石，还有我们的小厨房里有肉桂和肉豆蔻的味道。有很多东西可以享受！^^亲爱的，别在矿井里呆得太晚。里面很危险！如果你非得去……要带上足够的食物。^^——爱你的，艾利欧特 [#]Letter From My Husband 5 / 我丈夫的信 5",
        "SandyCooking": "Dear @,^I was so bored out here in the desert that I wrote you a letter. There's a recipe for a delicious soup enclosed. Come visit me soon! ^   -Sandy%item cookingRecipe %% / 亲爱的@：^我在沙漠里好无聊，所以给你写了这封信。随信附上一种靓汤的配方。赶紧来看看我吧！^——桑迪 [#]Sandy's Recipe / 桑迪的配方",
        "summer_6_2": "Fisherman Wanted^I need a good pufferfish specimen. I'm conducting an experiment on the toxin created by the pufferfish.^Reward: 1000g^ -Demetrius%item quest 118 %% / 招聘渔夫^需要一条完美的河豚标本。我在进行河豚毒素的实验。^奖励：1,000 金^——德米特里厄斯 [#]Demetrius' Study On Toxins / 德米特里厄斯的毒素实验",
        "Gus": "@!^I made you a little treat this morning in the saloon. Dig in!   ^   -Your friend, Gus%item id (O)224 1 (O)213 1 (O)211 1 (O)207 1 (O)200 1 (O)195 1 (O)198 1 %% / @！^今天早上我在酒吧里给你做了些好吃的。来吃吧！^—你的朋友，格斯 [#]A Gift From Gus / 来自格斯的礼物",
        "EvelynCooking": "Dear @,^I usually don't give out my recipes... but since you've been such a sweetheart to George and I, I've written this one down for you. ^   -Evelyn%item cookingRecipe %% / 亲爱的@：^我一般不把我的配方告诉别人……但是你对我和乔治都太好了，所以我把这份配方送给你。 ^——艾芙琳 [#]Evelyn's Recipe / 艾芙琳的配方",
        "fall_3_1": "Dear @,^I'd like to give my cows a special treat. They're such good girls and hungry, too. Could you bring me one bunch of amaranth? They love the stuff. ^Thanks, Dear.^   -Marnie %item quest 106 %% / 亲爱的@：^我想给我的奶牛们搞些好吃的。这些奶牛棒极了，就是有点饿，你能帮我搞到一把苋菜么。它们很爱苋菜。^麻烦你了，亲爱的。^——玛妮 [#]Marnie's Request / 玛妮的请求",
        "willyBugWadCutscene": "^^   -Willy%item craftingRecipe Quality_Bobber %% / ^^——威利 [#]Willy's Thank-you / 威利的感谢",
        "spring_21_2": "NOTICE^Pierre here... I really, really want a plate of sashimi. I'll pay top coin to whoever brings me some.^   -Pierre%item quest 117 %% / 通知^皮埃尔有话要说……我想吃生鱼片想疯了。谁给我带一点生鱼片我会给他报酬的。^——皮埃尔 [#]Pierre's Craving / 皮埃尔的渴求",
        "MarniePetRejectedAdoption": "Dear @,^^I hope this letter finds you well.^^I know you decided against adopting a pet when I last asked. However, if you've changed your mind, I am now offering pet adoptions from my shop.^^See you around!^-Marnie / 亲爱的@：^^最近过得还顺利吗？^^上次我问你要不要领养宠物，你拒绝了。不过没关系，我会在店里提供宠物领养，如果你回心转意了可以来看看。^^回头见！^——玛妮 [#]Pet Adoptions Letter / 关于宠物领养的信",
        "incubator": "Dear @,^^Thank you for purchasing a coop upgrade! In addition to doubling the capacity of your coop, I've taken the liberty of installing an incubator. ^To use the incubator, simply place an egg inside. If you have space left in your coop, the egg will hatch in several days!^^As always, thanks for your business.^-Robin / 亲爱的@：^^感谢你选择购买鸡舍升级服务！我不仅让你的鸡舍容量翻了一番，我还帮你安装了孵化器。^你只要把鸡蛋放入孵化器即可。只要你的鸡舍还有位置，过不了几天鸡蛋就会孵化啦。^^很感谢您的光临。^——罗宾 [#]About The Incubator / 关于孵化器",
        "EmilyDoneCamping": "Thanks for joining me last night... I had a great time.^I'm actually glad that bear showed up!^^See you soon^^  Love, Emily / 昨晚，谢谢你赴约……我度过了一段美好的时光。^我真的很感激熊的出现！^^再见^^爱你，艾米丽 [#]Emily's Note / 艾米丽的笔记",
        "LewisCooking": "@,^remember to eat healthy, or you won't have enough energy to work hard! I'm including one of my favorite recipes. Make sure to use ripe tomatoes! ^   -Lewis%item cookingRecipe %% / @：^要注意健康饮食，才能有足够的体力工作！随信附上一份我最爱的配方。记着要用熟的西红柿。^——刘易斯 [#]Lewis's Recipe / 刘易斯的配方",
        "fall_26": "Dear @,^Notice a chill in the air? It could just be the approach of winter...^Or it could be the tingle of a dark specter, here to help us celebrate tomorrow's festival... the Spirit's Eve.^Come to town at 10 PM if you'd like to participate.^  -Mayor Lewis / 亲爱的@：^不知道你有没有注意到寒气，冬天可能要来了……^不然就是黑暗的游魂，呼啸着和我们一起庆祝今天的节日……万灵节！^晚上 10 点来镇里和我们一起庆祝吧。^——镇长刘易斯 [#]Spirit's Eve Notice / 万灵节通知",
        "passedOut3_Billed": "@,^Someone dropped you off at the clinic last night. You'd passed out from exhaustion!^You've got to take better care of yourself and go to bed at a reasonable hour.^I've billed you {0}g to cover your medical expenses.^^-Dr. Harvey / @：^昨晚有人将你送到诊所了。你因中暑而晕倒！^你要照顾好自己，并在合适的时间及时睡觉。^你的医疗费是 {0} 金。^^——哈维医生 [#]From The Office Of Dr. Harvey / 来自哈维医生的办公室",
        "dad3": "Dear @,^  I read an article about you in the local paper! I'm so impressed with your progress on the farm! Keep this up and dear old Dad might be retiring in a fern islands luxury bungalow after all ;).^  Love, Dad / 亲爱的@：^我在报纸上有看到你的报道！你竟然变得那么优秀了！继续加油，说不定你爹可以在热带小岛上，住着小房子，过着奢侈的退休生活呢！^爱你的爸爸 [#]From Dad #3 / 爸爸的信 #3",
        "willyBackRoomInvitation": "@,^^I've unlocked the back room of the shop.^Come by when you have a chance.^There's something I want to show you.^^-Willy / @：^^我把商店后面的里屋打开了。^如果有空的话请过来一下。^我有点东西想给你看看。^^——威利 [#]Willy's Back Room Invitation / 威利邀请去里屋",
        "EmilyClothingTherapy": "@,^I have this crazy new idea that I want to involve you in... It's called \"Clothing Therapy\".^^Please come to the Mayor's house today to see what it's all about.^^ Love, Emily / @，^我有了一个疯狂的新想法，我想你了解……所谓的“服装疗法”。^^请在今天去镇长的家里，了解它是关于什么的。^^爱你，艾米丽 [#]Emily's Idea / 艾米丽的想法",
        "Sandy": "Greetings from Calico Desert!^Come visit me soon, I'm really bored out here :(. I've included a gift from the desert. You can come and thank me in person!   ^   -Sandy %item id (O)88 1 (O)90 1 (O)218 1 %% / 这是来自卡利科沙漠的问候！^赶紧来看看我吧，我在这儿好无聊：（随信附上一份来自沙漠的礼物。你可以亲自来向我道谢！^——桑迪 [#]A Gift From Sandy / 来自桑迪的礼物",
        "Beat_PK": "Congratulations!!^^You beat 'Journey Of The Prairie King', and were randomly selected in our exclusive winner's sweepstakes! ^You've won a Prairie King Arcade System of your very own!^Now you can enjoy 'Journey Of The Prairie King' from the comfort of your own home.^^You deserve it!^-Prairie King Development Team %item id (BC)141 %% / 恭喜你！！！^^你通关了“草原之王的冒险之旅”并被我们选为特别奖励获得者！^你赢得了专属于你自己的草原之王的冒险之旅游戏系统！^现在你可以在家享受“草原之王的冒险之旅”带来的乐趣！^^这是你的奖赏！^——草原之王的冒险之旅开发团队 [#]P.K. Congratulations! / 草原之王的冒险之旅的祝贺",
        "adoptionLetter": "Dear @ and spouse,^Congratulations! Your adoption application has been approved.^We're working hard to choose the perfect baby to match your profile.^Your new family member will arrive in 2 weeks.^^-Ferngill Adoption Agency / 亲爱的@和您的爱人。^衷心地祝贺你！你的收养申请已通过审查！^我们现在正努力为您挑选与您相配的完美婴儿。^小宝宝会在两周内和你们见面。^^——芬吉尔领养机构 [#]Adoption Notice / 领养通知",
        "WillyCooking": "Dear @,^I'd like to share an ol' cooking recipe my pappy used to make. It's important the fish is FRESH.  ^   -Willy%item cookingRecipe %% / 亲爱的@：^我想分享爸爸曾经发明的一道菜肴。其中的精髓就在于鱼要百分百新鲜！ ^——威利 [#]Willy's Ol' Recipe / 威利的配方",
        "WizardReward": "The specimen you delivered offered great insight into the machinations of the fell beings we call 'monsters'.^^I've formulated a pungent tincture that these beings find intoxicating. Use it with caution...^^   -M. Rasmodius, Wizard%item craftingRecipe Monster_Musk %% / 你提供的标本让我深入了解了我们称之为“怪物”的堕落生物的阴谋。^^我配置了一种气味刺激的药酒，可以让这些怪物陶醉，使用时要小心……^^——法师 M·拉斯莫迪斯 [#]The Wizard's Discovery / 法师的发现",
        "dad2": "Dear @,^  How is the country life going for you? It's been lonely here without you, but I'm proud of what you're doing.^  Love, Dad  ^  P.S. Found an envelope with some money Grandpa left for you. %item money 500 501 %% / 亲爱的@：^乡下生活还适应吗？虽然你不在我身边了，但是我一直为你感到自豪。^爱你的爸爸 ^我收拾到一个装着一些钱的信封，那是你爷爷留下来给你的。 [#]From Dad #2 / 爸爸的信 #2",
        "SeaAmulet": "@,^I'm going to give you this advice because I like you and I want you to stay in Pelican Town. If there comes a day that you want to ask for someone's hand in marriage, you'll need to give them a 'Mermaid's Pendant'. Don't worry, everyone in Pelican Town understands the significance of the amulet. It's an ancient tradition in this region. Good luck! ^   -Lewis / @：^我喜欢你而且想让你留在鹈鹕镇，所以我想给你一个建议。如果有一天你想向人求婚的话，你需要给那个人一个“美人鱼吊坠”。别担心，鹈鹕镇的居民都知道护身符的重要性。这是这片地方的古老传统。祝您好运！^——刘易斯 [#]About Mermaid's Pendants / 关于美人鱼吊坠",
        "emilyStones": "Hi @,^^Thanks again for the wonderful gemstones.^These will be perfect for my energy re-alignment work!^I wanted to thank you with this special gift. I hope you create some wonderful items with it!^^-Emily%item id (BC)247 %% / @：^^你好。再次感谢你送给我的宝石，它们品质很好。^我的能量调息用这些宝石正正好好！^我想用这份特别的礼物表示我的感谢。希望你能用它做出更多好东西！^^——艾米丽 [#]Emily's Gemstones / 艾米丽的宝石",
        "CarolineCooking": "Dear @,^Nothing is more satisfying than cooking with fresh vegetables from your own garden! I've enclosed a recipe to help you out. Take care, ^   -Caroline%item cookingRecipe %% / 亲爱的@：^没有什么能比用自己种的菜做饭更让人满足的了！我随信附上了一份食谱。照顾好自己。 ^—卡洛琳 [#]Caroline's Recipe / 卡洛琳的食谱",
        "wizardJunimoNote": "My sources tell me you've been poking around inside the old community center.^Why don't you pay me a visit?^My chambers are west of the forest lake, in the stone tower. I may have information concerning your... 'rat problem'.^   -M. Rasmodius, Wizard %item quest 1 true %% / 我的信息源告诉我，你一直在旧社区活动中心附近溜达。^何不来拜访我一趟？^我住在森林湖西边的石塔里。关于你那……“老鼠肆虐”的问题，我也许有一些线索。^——法师 M·拉斯莫迪斯 [#]Wizard's Summons / 法师的召集",
        "ccBulletinThankYou": "Dear @,^Everyone around town has been talking about your great generosity lately!^Apparently, packages have been appearing in people's houses containing items they posted about years ago on the community center bulletin! And the packages are all addressed from your farm!^Thanks for going out of your way to do something like that... all of us in town are delighted! ^   -Mayor Lewis / 亲爱的@：^最近镇上的乡亲都在褒扬你的大方呢！^最近，人们都收到了不同的包裹，包裹里都是他们很早之前在社区活动中心公告栏里求购的东西。这些包裹都是从你的农场寄出的！^真的很感激你高尚的行为，乡亲们都很开心！^——镇长刘易斯 [#]Bulletin Board Thank-you / 公告栏的感谢",
        "guntherBones": "Hi @,^^Thanks for all the bones. I've got a lot to sort through here! To think, each fragment belonged to a living, breathing body from the past. Fascinating.^^Please accept this unique crafting recipe as a thank-you gift!^^-Gunther%item craftingRecipe Bone_Mill %% / @：^^你好。谢谢你提供的骨头。它们正等着我去研究！你想想，每一块骨头都曾属于一个活着的远古生命，多么迷人。^^这是给你的感谢礼物，请收下这份独特的工艺配方！^^——冈瑟 [#]Gunther's Note / 冈瑟的便条",
        "passedOutIsland": "@,^^You never showed up at the boat, so I went lookin' for ya.^^Found you sprawled out in the dirt, with a couple o' parrots pulling gold out of your pockets!^^Had to drag you all the way down to the boat. Me legs feel like two freshwater shrimp...^-Willy / @：^^在船上没发现你，所以我就去找你了。^^结果发现你躺在泥里，而且还有几只鹦鹉正从你口袋里掏金币！^^之后我一路把你拖回了船上。现在我的腿软得跟虾一样……^——威利",
        "samMessage": "@,^meet me in front of my house tonight after dark. ^   -Sam / @：^天黑后在我家门前等我 ^——山姆 [#]Sam's Note / 山姆的笔记",
        "pennySpa": "Meet me in the bath house after dark. ^   -Penny / 晚上到澡堂来见我 ^——潘妮 [#]Penny's Note / 潘妮的笔记",
        "Rabbits": "Dear @,^I now have rabbits in the animal shop! They will provide you with fluffy wool ...and more!       ^   -Marnie / 亲爱的@：^现在我的动物商店里有兔子！它们能为你提供松软的兔毛……和其他东西！^——玛妮 [#]Rabbits For Sale! / 兔子开始售卖！",
        "fishing2": "I've got some new items in stock...^A deluxe fishing pole and some bait that you can attach to it!^You can use bait to make fish bite faster. Hope to see you soon! ^   -Willy / 我进了一些新货品！^豪华钓竿，你可以在上面放置饵料！^你可以使用饵料让鱼更快地上钩！欢迎前来购买！^——威利 [#]Willy's New Items / 威利的新货品",
        "winter_26_1": "Dear @-^I want to make fish stew, but I need an albacore! I know they're almost out of season... sorry about the short notice. Could you catch one for me?^   -Gus%item quest 114 %% / 亲爱的@：^我想要炖一锅鱼！我知道这个季节不好找……突然这样拜托你有点强人所难。但是你能帮我抓到一条回来吗？^——格斯 [#]Gus Needs A Certain Fish / 格斯需要一种鱼",
        "elliottLetter1": "@, my love,^^I've just arrived in Grampleton, to start the tour. I've forgotten how hectic the city is! The streets are packed with people... they either seem in a mad hurry, or lost in a daze, unaware of their surroundings. I miss Pelican Town already!^^I begin the tour this evening, at a local bookstore. I must admit, I'm becoming a bit nervous at the thought of public speaking... my stomach feels as if it's been twisted into a soft pretzel and doused with spicy cheese dip. Wish me luck!^^-Love, Elliott^^P.S. I hope you had a peaceful night, and weren't too scared all alone in that big house! %item conversationTopic ElliottGone2 0 %% / 亲爱的@：^^我刚到格兰普立顿开始巡回。我都忘了这座城市有多繁忙！街道上挤满了人……他们要么看起来很匆忙，要么迷茫，对周围的环境毫无感觉。我已经开始怀念鹈鹕镇了！^^我今晚在当地的一家书店开始阅读会。我必须承认，一想到要公开演讲，我就有点紧张……我的胃感觉好像被拧成了一个柔软的椒盐脆饼，蘸上了辛辣的奶酪。祝我好运！^^——爱你的，艾利欧特^^附：我希望你度过了一个平静的夜晚，一个人在大房子里不要害怕！ [#]Letter From My Husband / 我丈夫的信",
        "summer_20_1": "@-^I'm gathering data on the correlation between soil alkalinity and crop fructose levels. Long story short, I need a fresh melon from your farm. If you brought me one I'd be very grateful.^   -Demetrius%item quest 104 %% / @：^我在收集数据以验证土地酸碱度和作物果糖浓度的关系。简单地说，我需要一颗来自你的农场的甜瓜。如果你能送一个给我的话，我会非常感激的。^——德米特里厄斯 [#]Demetrius Asks For A Sample / 德米特里厄斯请求样本",
        "Goats": "Dear @,^I now have goats available for purchase at the animal shop. You've done well so far!       ^   -Marnie / 亲爱的@：^现在我的动物商店里有山羊出售！到目前为止你做得很好！^——玛妮 [#]Goats For Sale! / 山羊开始售卖！",
        "Demetrius": "Dear @,^I was conducting a field study the other day, and I found this specimen. ^I hope you find it as interesting as I did.    ^   -Demetrius%item id (O)392 1 (O)394 1 (O)132 1 (O)66 1 %% / 亲爱的@：^我前几天做了次实地考察，然后发现了这个标本。^我希望你和我一样对它感兴趣。 ^——德米特里厄斯 [#]A Gift From Demetrius / 来自德米特里厄斯的礼物",
        "Pierre": "Dear valued customer,^Thanks for visiting 'Pierre's'! Enclosed is your 'Cash-back Rewards Program' rebate. See you soon! ^   -Pierre^  P.S. Sorry for the stock message, @. Enjoy! %item money 250 601 %% / 尊敬的客户：^感谢您对皮埃尔商店的惠顾！随信附上“返利计划”的退款。祝好！^——皮埃尔^附:股份信息给您带来诸多不便，还请谅解，@。祝您生活愉快！ [#]A Gift From Pierre / 来自皮埃尔的礼物",
        "passedOut1_NotBilled_Female": "Dear Ms. @,^Last night, a Joja team member found you incapacitated. A medical team was dispatched to bring you home safely.^We're glad you're okay!^^Since you have no money, we were obligated by law to provide this service free of charge.^^-Morris^Joja Customer Satisfaction Representative / 亲爱的@小姐！^昨晚，Joja 团队的一位员工发现您昏倒了。我们派出了一支医疗小队来把您安全地送回了家里。^很高兴您没有出事！^^由于您没有钱，根据法律我们有义务向您提供免费服务。^^——莫里斯^Joja 顾客满意部门代表 [#]Legally Required Notice / 法律要求的通知",
        "RarecrowSociety": "Dear @,^^Your dedication is truly impressive...^^Only a select few manage to acquire the complete Rarecrow collection!^^Please accept this blueprint to commemorate your achievement.^   -The Z.C. Rarecrow Society%item craftingRecipe Deluxe_Scarecrow %% / 亲爱的@：^^您的贡献令人赞叹……^^只有少数人能够收集全套珍奇乌鸦系列！！^^请收下这张图纸以纪念你的成就。^   ——Z.C. 珍奇乌鸦协会 [#]From The Rarecrow Society / 珍奇乌鸦协会来信",
        "PierreCooking": "TOP SECRET:^Here's the recipe for my famous blueberry tart.^Don't tell anyone! I'm giving it to you because we are such good friends. ^   -Pierre%item cookingRecipe %% / 最高机密：^这是我著名的蓝莓挞配方。^别告诉任何人哦！我之所以把它给你，是因为你是我的好朋友。 ^——皮埃尔 [#]Pierre's Famous Tart / 皮埃尔的著名蓝莓挞",
        "JunimoKart": "Congratulations!!^^You beat all the levels in 'JunimoKart'... you're actually the first person in the entire Ferngill Republic to do so!^Your prize: a home version of Junimo Kart!^^Have fun!^-Junimo Kart Development Team %item id (BC)159 %% / 恭喜你！！！^^你通关了，你是芬吉尔共和国第一个通过的人！^你的奖励：一台家庭版的祝尼魔赛车！^^好好享受游戏！^——祝尼魔赛车开发团队 [#]Junimo Kart Success! / 祝尼魔赛车通关！",
        "dad4": "Dear @,^ I know you're busy on the farm and that's why you can't visit. I understand. You've been working so hard... keep it up and you can accomplish anything! ^ Love, Dad  ^  P.S. Included some quality stone %item id (O)390 30 %% / 亲爱的@：^听说你在农场忙的都没法来探望我们，没事我们理解的，你一直都那么努力……世上无难事，只怕有心人，加油！^爱你的爸爸 ^附：我给你寄了些很棒的石头 [#]From Dad #4 / 爸爸的信 #4",
        "MarlonRecovery": "@,^Found your lost item.^^Be more careful next time!^   -Marlon%item itemRecovery %% / @：^你丢失的物品找到了。^^下次细心点！^   ——马龙 [#]Marlon Found Your Item / 马龙找到了你的东西",
        "MarniePetAdoption": "Dear @,^^From what I can tell, you've been taking really good care of your pet! I'm really happy about that!^^But there are many sweet animals that need a home... If you're interested, I'll start offering pet adoptions at my shop.^^Just be aware that there is a licensing fee, and also that each pet will want their own outdoor pet bowl area, or else they'll be unhappy. Robin will be happy to construct additional pet bowls, for a price.^^See you soon!^-Marnie / 亲爱的@：^^据我了解，你把家里的宠物照顾得非常好！我真的很惊喜！^^可是还是有很多可爱的动物需要一个家……我会在店里提供宠物领养，你感兴趣的话可以来看看。^^需要注意，办理饲养证需要一定费用，并且每只宠物都需要专属的宠物碗区域，否则它们会不高兴。宠物碗可以付费请罗宾安装。^^回头见！^——玛妮 [#]Pet Adoptions Letter / 关于宠物领养的信",
        "summer_3_1": "@-^This is embarrassing... I lost my lucky purple shorts. I'm telling you because I think I can trust you.^If you find them, bring them back to me DISCREETLY. I'll pay well.^Thanks.^   -Mayor Lewis%item quest 102 %% / @：^这有点尴尬了。我把我的幸运紫色短裤丢了。我只告诉你，因为我信任你。^如果你能帮我找到，请妥善归还。我会给你丰富报酬的哦。^麻烦你了。^——镇长刘易斯 [#]Lewis Asks For A Favor / 刘易斯需要帮助",
        "spring_15_2": "Dear @,^I'd like to surprise my husband with a gift. He's a big fan of leeks. Could you bring me one?^   -Granny Evelyn%item quest 116 %% / 亲爱的@：^我想给我的丈夫一份特别的礼物。他特别喜欢大葱，你可以给我点么？^——艾芙琳奶奶 [#]Evelyn's Surprise / 艾芙琳的惊喜",
        "George": "Found some good quality stone. ^Maybe you can build with it or something.  ^   -George %item id (O)390 35 %% / 我找到了一些优质石材。^也许你能用它建点儿什么。 ^——乔治 [#]A Gift From George / 来自乔治的礼物",
        "joshMessage": "@,^meet me at the saloon tonight after dark. ^   -Alex / @：^天黑后到酒馆见我。 ^——亚历克斯 [#]Alex' Invitation / 亚历克斯的邀请",
        "JodiCooking": "@,^this recipe of mine won 1st place in a cooking competition! I hope you like it. Thanks for being a friend! ^   -Jodi%item cookingRecipe %% / @：^这份食谱曾帮我在烹饪比赛里赢得第一名！希望你喜欢。就算是朋友的谢礼吧！^——乔迪 [#]Jodi's Recipe / 乔迪的配方",
        "fishing6": "Come by the shop and check out the new rods I'm selling.^They're the best money can buy... and you can customize them with different kinds of tackle!^Hope to see you soon! ^   -Willy / 快来看一看瞧一瞧，新品鱼竿上市咯。^货真价实，你还可以装备不同的钓具！^欢迎前来选购！^——威利 [#]Willy's New Items #2 / 威利的新货品 #2",
        "elliottLetter4": "In dreams, when graced with lofty view^I gaze upon the sunlit sea^What distant shores I've traveled to^But time now clouds my memory^^There is but one eternal place^Where I shall someday pass beyond^In Valley dear, where my love waits:^Our little home beside the pond^^-Elliott %item conversationTopic ElliottGone5 0 %% / 在梦中，当我仰望远眺时^我凝视着阳光照耀的大海^凝视着我所走过的遥远的海岸^但时间模糊了我的记忆^^永恒的地方只有一个^我总有一天会经过那里^是在可爱的山谷里，有我的爱人在等待：^我们在池塘边的小家^^——艾利欧特 [#]Letter From My Husband 4 / 我丈夫的信 4",
        "pierreHours": "ADVERTISEMENT:^^Pierre's General Store is now open 7 days a week! / 广告：^^皮埃尔商店每周 7 天都不休息！ [#]Pierre's Extended Hours / 皮埃尔商店延长时间",
        "ClintCooking": "Well, I know a couple of recipes.^I thought I'd send you one... maybe it'll help you mine more ore or something.^Take care. ^   -Clint%item cookingRecipe %% / 嗯，我倒是知道两三种配方。^告诉你一种的话……或许能帮你多开采些矿石也说不定。^保重。 ^——克林特 [#]Clint's Recipe / 克林特的配方",
        "winter_14": "Starting tomorrow, a traveling merchant fleet will dock at Pelican Town for the yearly night market.^^The market starts at 5pm, and will be in port for the next three days.^^Please visit the beach after 5pm to join the festivities. There's free coffee! / 从明天开始，一个旅行商队将在鹈鹕镇停留，以参加每年一次的夜市。^^夜市从下午 5 时开始，并在接下来的三天内在港口内举行。^^下午 5 时后请到海滩参加庆祝活动。有免费咖啡！ [#]Night Market Notice / 夜市通知",
        "willyHours": "Good news!^^The ol' boat is seaworthy once again, thanks to you!^^Stop by the back room whenever you want a ride.^^My shop is now open at 8AM every day, so you can get an early start.^^-Willy / 好消息！^^多亏了你，这艘船又能出海了！^^你想出航的话随时到里屋来就行。^^我的店现在每天早上 8 点开门，所以你想早点出发也可以。^^——威利 [#]Willy's Boat / 威利的船",
        "mom2": "Dear @,^  It's been so long since I heard from you, dear. Things are the same as ever back home. I miss you very much. ^  Love, Mom ^ P.S. Found an envelope with some money Grandpa left for you. %item money 500 501 %% / 亲爱的@：^很久没收到你的来信了。家里还是和回来的时候一样。我非常想你。^爱你的妈妈。 ^我收拾到一个装着一些钱的信封，那是你爷爷留下来给你的。 [#]From Mom #2 / 妈妈的信 #2",
        "DemetriusCooking": "I wanted to say 'thanks' for taking an interest in my work. Here's a cooking recipe that I like. ^   -Demetrius%item cookingRecipe %% / 德米特里厄斯我想感谢你对我工作的支持。这是一份我喜欢的烹饪食谱。 ^——德米特里厄斯 [#]Demetrius' Recipe / 德米特里厄斯的食谱",
        "spring_15_1": "Hello, dear...^^I know you're just getting started as a gardener, so I wanted to give you a little tip.^^Most crops only grow in one season. When summer arrives, your spring crops will all die out. So plan ahead!^^-Granny Evelyn / 你好呀，亲爱的……^^我了解到你刚刚开始种菜，所以我想给你一个小小的提示。^^大多数作物只能生长一季。等夏天到了的时候，你在春天种的所有作物就都会枯萎。所以你要提前计划好！^^——艾芙琳奶奶 [#]Evelyn's Tip / 艾芙琳的提示",
        "winter_6_1": "I've got an unusual request. Could you keep this a secret?^ I want you to deliver an amethyst to Emily. It's her favorite stone. Tell her it's from me.^   -Clint %item quest 110 %% / 我有个特殊的请求。你可以不跟别人说嘛？^帮我把紫水晶交给艾米丽。这是她最喜爱的宝石。记得跟她说是我送她的。^——克林特 [#]Clint's Unusual Request / 克林特特殊请求",
        "quest10": "@,^I've heard you've been giving some people a hand around town! Everyone seems really thankful. I'm awarding you this month's \"Best Neighbor\" award (with a small cash prize). Keep it up! ^   -Mayor%item money 500 501 %% / @：^我听说你最近一直对镇上的人们施以援手！大家都很感激你！因此我想把本月的“最佳邻居”奖授予你（同时你会获得一点现金鼓励）。继续努力吧！^——镇长 [#]Best Neighbor / 最佳邻居",
        "elliottLetter6": "My dear @,^^This will be my last letter before I return home. I've had a fine trip... though nothing too exciting. It's been nice to meet people who enjoy my work, but I'm eager to return home.^^I look forward to the comfort of our little house, the satisfying farm work, a home-cooked meal, and most of all, cozying into the flannel sheets with you.^^See you soon!^-Love, Elliott %item conversationTopic ElliottGone7 0 %% / 亲爱的@：^^这是我回家前的最后一封信了。我的旅程十分愉快……虽然没什么十分激动人心的事情。能见到喜欢我的书的人让我很高兴，但我还是渴望回家。^^我想念我们舒适的小房子，令人满足的农活，一顿家常菜，当然最想念的，是和你一起舒适地躺在法兰绒的床单上。^^盼早日见到你！^——爱你的，艾利欧特 [#]Letter From My Husband 6 / 我丈夫的信 6",
        "summer_14_1": "Hey Kid,^My throat's about as dry as a desert bone. I'm real thirsty for a pale ale. You got one? Regular old beer won't do. I need a pale ale.^   -Pam%item quest 103 %% / 孩子你好，^我的喉咙要干透了。我真的很渴望喝一点淡啤酒。你有淡啤酒吗？普通的老啤酒不会有用的。一定要是淡啤酒啊。^-潘姆 [#]Pam's Request / 潘姆的请求",
        "EmilyCooking": "@!^Flip this letter over for instructions on how to make a super-healthy meal!^You'll feel energized. See you soon. ^   -Emily%item cookingRecipe %% / @！^把这封信翻过来，上面写有一种超级健康的饭菜做法！^那会让你感觉精力充沛。那一会见咯！ ^——艾米丽 [#]Emily's Healthy Recipe / 艾米丽的健康食谱",
        "spring_23": "Dear @,^Tomorrow we're all getting together for the Flower Dance.^^If you can find a partner, you might even want to participate in the dance yourself!^There's a little clearing beyond the forest west of town where we hold the dance. Arrive between 9 AM and 2 PM if you're interested.^  -Mayor Lewis / 亲爱的@：^明天就是花舞节了！^^你可以邀请一位舞伴，和我们一起起舞。^我们会在小镇西边森林后的空地举行舞会。如果你感兴趣，请在上午 9 点到下午 2 点出席。^——镇长刘易斯 [#]Flower Dance Notice / 花舞节通知",
        "winter_2_1": "Hey, I've got a little challenge for you:^    Catch me a squid.^You can fish them from the ocean at night. They only show up in the winter, though.^   -Willy%item quest 109 %% / 嘿，帮我个忙吧：^    帮我抓只鱿鱼。^你可以晚上去大海里面找找。不过他们只在冬天出现。^——威利 [#]Willy's Challenge / 威利的挑战",
        "mom1": "Dear @,^  How are you doing, sweety? I've missed you so much since you left. I hope the farming life is everything you hoped for. ^   Love, Mom.   ^   P.S. I sent your favorite cookies < %item id (O)223 1 %% / 亲爱的@：^宝贝，你最近过的怎么样？你走了我真是朝思夜想。我希望农场上的生活是你期望的那样。^爱你的妈妈。^附：我把你最喜欢的饼干寄给你了。 [#]From Mom / 妈妈的信",
        "lewisStatue": "@,^^In the future, I'd appreciate it very much if you refrained from placing my PRIVATE belongings in town for all to see!^^I'm very displeased!^^Take this money and never speak of my 'project' to anyone.%item money 750 751 %% / @，^^今后，如果你能不把我的私人物品放在城里让所有人都看到，我会非常感激！^^我很不高兴！^^拿上这笔钱，不要向任何人提起我的“项目”。 [#]Lewis' Angry Letter / 刘易斯的抱怨信",
        "elliottReading": "@,^I have great news... my novel is finished!! I'm giving a public reading this afternoon at the library. Hope to see you there! ^   -Elliott / @：^我有个天大的好消息……我写完我的小说了！我下午会在图书馆前举行一个公开的阅读会。你一定要来！^——艾利欧特 [#]Elliott's Reading / 艾利欧特的阅读会",
        "georgeGifts": "Dear @,^^Thank you so much for the leeks. They look fresh and delicious. George will love them.^^Today, I'm going to surprise him with 12 little gift-wrapped treasures (thanks to you!). Stop by if you want to be there!^^-Evelyn^^P.S. Please accept this gift. I think you'll enjoy it!%item id (BC)246 %% / 亲爱的@：^^谢谢你送来的韭葱，看起来新鲜而且美味。乔治会喜欢的。^^今天我要用 12 份包装好的小礼物给他一个惊喜！（多亏有你帮忙！）你可以过来看看！^^——艾芙琳^^附：请收下这份礼物，你会喜欢的！ [#]Evelyn's thank-you note / 艾芙琳的感谢信",
        "KentCooking": "Picked up this recipe overseas. Enjoy.^Want to say thanks for making me feel welcome. ^^   -Kent%item cookingRecipe %% / 我是在国外发现的这份配方。尽情品尝吧。^我想要对你的好客说声谢谢。 ^^——肯特 [#]Kent's Recipe / 肯特的配方",
        "pierreBackpack": "ADVERTISEMENT:^\"I keep finding cool stuff, but my backpack is full!\"^^Does this sound like you? Well, Pierre's got you covered!^^Stop by Pierre's General Store TODAY and check out our affordable size 24 backpack!^ See you soon! / 广告：^虽然我的背包已经装不下了，但我还是在继续寻找更酷的东西！^^是不是很像你？哈哈，有皮埃尔在就高枕无忧了。^^今天光临皮埃尔商店，看看价廉物美的 24 号背包！^祝好！ [#]Backpacks From Pierre's / 皮埃尔商店的背包",
        "winter_19_2": "Dear @,^I'm at my wit's end. I desperately want to make a Coco-no-no at the saloon, but I have no way of getting a coconut!^Can you help me?^  -Gus%item quest 125 %% / 亲爱的@：^我束手无策了。我想在我的酒吧调一杯椰子酒，但是我不知道怎么才能搞到椰子！^你能帮帮我么？^——格斯 [#]Gus Needs A Coconut / 格斯需要椰子",
        "pamNewChannel": "Hey kid,^^Thanks for the 'juice'. It definitely had a ...one-of-a-kind... flavor.^^By the way, have you ever tuned in to channel 736? It's a seasonal fishing program that you might find interesting.^^Take care,^-Pam / 孩子，你好：^^感谢你的“果汁”。它的确有一种……“独特”的风味^^顺便问一下，你有没有看过 736 频道？是一个季节性捕捞节目，你可能感兴趣。^^多多保重。^——潘姆 [#]Pam's Tip / 潘姆的提示",
        "elliottLetter3": "My sweet @,^^Last night in Zuzu City was quite the experience! It seems there's a large literary scene here... a few dozen people showed up at my reading!^^I even signed a couple of autographs... it's strange to be seen as someone important. It's all a matter of framing, a grand illusion... for truly I am no one special. Only your devoted Elliott, as always.^^Currently I'm alone, in my hotel room, 'ingesting' a Joja Value Meal...^^Should this be called 'food'?^Or 'edible matter'?^I needn't long brood^It must be the latter^^I look forward to returning home soon. Hope you enjoyed the crab cakes.^^-Love, Elliott %item conversationTopic ElliottGone4 0 %% / 我亲爱的@：^^昨晚在祖祖城的经历十分棒！看起来是一个巨大的文学集会……我的读书会上有几十个人！^^我甚至签了几张签名……被看做知名人士让我感觉很别扭。这只是一个错觉……事实上我一点也不特别。只是你挚爱的艾利欧特，一如既往。^^现在我独自一人，在我的酒店房间，“摄入”了一顿 Joja 超值餐……^^这应该叫“食物”还是“可食用的物质”？^不用多想^肯定是后者^^我期待能够早点回家，希望你喜欢蟹黄糕。^^——爱你的，艾利欧特 [#]Letter From My Husband 3 / 我丈夫的信 3",
        "spring_6_2": "@-^I'm really craving a fresh apricot. I haven't been able to find one at the store, so I'm asking you. I'll pay you well for it!^   -Emily%item quest 115 %% / @——^我好想要一个新鲜的杏子啊。但是商店里没有卖的，如果你能帮我弄到的话。我会给你很多报酬的！^——艾米丽 [#]Emily's Request / 艾米丽的请求",
        "GreenRainGus": "Saw the weather report last night.^^I'm not sure what will happen, but if anyone wants to take shelter in the Saloon, I'll keep it open all day.^^-Gus / 我看了昨晚的天气预报。^^不知道会发生什么事，我明天会全天开放酒吧，大家可以来避难。^^——格斯 [#]Shelter In The Saloon / 酒吧避难所",
        "MSB_Lewis": "@,^I wanted to thank you for taking care of my special order. All of the hard work you've done has been a great boost to Pelican Town's image.^Here's a 'Mini-Shipping Bin' as a token of my appreciation.^Place it anywhere and I'll be sure to make a stop when I make my rounds.^^   -Lewis%item id (BC)248 %% / @：^感谢你帮我完成特别订单。你所付出的努力极大地提升了鹈鹕镇的形象。^给你一个“迷你出货箱”表达我对你的感谢。^把它放在哪里都行，轮到我巡视的时候一定会处理好的。^^——刘易斯 [#]Lewis's Thank You / 刘易斯的感谢",
        "spring_12": "Dear @,^Tomorrow we're holding the Egg Festival in the town square. ^^You should arrive between 9 AM and 2 PM if you'd like to attend.^You wouldn't want to miss the annual egg hunt!^  -Mayor Lewis / 亲爱的@：^明天我们会在广场欢庆复活节。^^如果你想和我们一起庆祝的话， 请在上午 9 点到下午 2 点之间到位。^一年一度的彩蛋大寻宝不容错过！^——镇长刘易斯 [#]Egg Festival Notice / 欢庆复活节通知",
        "winter_17_1": "@,^Sorry to bother you again, but I need another favor.^I got a new hammer and I want to try it on a variety of metals.^Could you smelt an iron bar and bring it to me? ^Thanks.^ -Clint %item quest 112 %% / @：^不好意思又来烦你了，但是我这次需要你来帮忙。^我想试试我的新铁锤敲不同金属会怎样。^你可以帮我炼一条铁锭给我么？^麻烦你了。^——克林特 [#]Clint's Request / 克林特的请求",
        "harveyBalloon": "@,^I have a surprise for you. Meet me by the railroad tracks. ^   -Harvey / @：^我想给你一个惊喜。在铁轨旁等我。 ^——哈维 [#]Harvey's Surprise / 哈维的惊喜",
        "passedOut1_Billed_Male": "Dear Mr. @,^Last night, a Joja team member found you incapacitated. A medical team was dispatched to bring you home safely.^We're glad you're okay!^^(You've been billed {0}g for this service)^^-Morris^Joja Customer Satisfaction Representative / 亲爱的@先生！^昨晚，Joja 团队的一位员工发现您昏倒了。我们派出了一支医疗小队来把您安全地送回了家里。^很高兴您没有出事！^^（这个服务会向您收取 {0} 金的费用）^^——莫里斯^Joja 顾客满意部门代表 [#]Joja Invoice / Joja 的账单",
        "MSB_Pierre": "Dear @,^^I guess people didn't take to 'Pierre's Prime Produce' like I'd hoped...^^Anyways, here's my old 'Mini-Shipping Bin'.^The next time you get your hands on some produce worthy of the 'Pierre's Prime' luxury brand, maybe you could have them shipped my way?^^   -Pierre%item id (BC)248 %% / 亲爱的@：^^似乎人们对我的“皮埃尔优选”不感兴趣，有点失望……^^不说了。这是我以前的“迷你出货箱”，给你。^下次你拿到配得上“皮埃尔优选”名号的产品的时候，考虑一下把它们卖到我这来？^^——皮埃尔 [#]Pierre's Prime Produce / 皮埃尔优选",
        "summer_25_1": "To Farmer @:^My knee's acting up again, and you know what helps? ^Rubbing the darn thing with hot pepper.^ Trouble is, my supply's run dry. If you've got one to spare I'd be much obliged.^   -George %item quest 105 %% / 致农夫@：^我的膝盖又疼了，你还有什么方子吗？^把辣椒抹在那该死的膝盖上。^问题是，我的储备已经空了。如果你有多余的辣椒可以给我的话，我会非常感激。^——乔治 [#]George Needs A Pepper / 乔治需要辣椒"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/TV/CookingChannel",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "1": "Stir Fry/Stir Fry! It's a perfect way to get some healthy greens on your plate. Sautee the greens in a little sesame oil and make sure to add plenty of fresh ginger and garlic. Now breathe deeply... Oh, that's good. / Stir Fry/蔬菜什锦盖饭！这是一种能吃到健康蔬菜的最佳方式。用少许芝麻油炒一下蔬菜，再加入足够的新鲜生姜和大蒜。现在，深吸一口气……嗷，味道果然很不错。",
        "21": "Carp Surprise/Hey, ever have a bunch of carp laying around and no idea what to do with them? Yeah, me too. Well, I've devised a great solution to this all-too-common problem. I call it... Carp surprise. It's quite easy to make, but you'll need a lot of carp...  / Carp Surprise/嘿，你是否有过一大堆鲤鱼，但又不知道如何来处理？嗯，我也是。好吧，我找到了一个方法，可以解决这个普遍存在的问题。我把它称作……惊喜鲤鱼。做起来很简单，但需要很多的鲤鱼……",
        "11": "Glazed Yams/Glazed Yams! It's yam season, and what better way to enjoy these delightful tubers than by slathering them in a sweet, sticky glaze? You'll need a nice, ripe yam and a whole bunch of sugar. Now, here's how you do it...  / Glazed Yams/琉璃山药！现在是吃山药的好时节，品尝这些可爱的块茎时，没有比抹上又甜又稠的糖浆更好的了吧？你只需要准备一根干净、成熟的山药和一把糖。现在，看我怎么来做……",
        "19": "Complete Breakfast/Complete Breakfast! Last week I taught you how to make hashbrowns. This week I'll show you how to combine them with other ingredients to create a hearty complete breakfast. This meal will really fill you up and give you the energy you need to get in a hard day's work. / Complete Breakfast/完美早餐！上周，我们教了你们如何制作土豆煎饼。这周，我要教你们如何将土豆煎饼和其它食材结合，做出一顿丰盛的爱心早餐。这个肉真的能填饱你的肚子，并且给你充足的能量，让你一整天工作都有劲。",
        "3": "Radish Salad/Radish Salad! There's nothing like a fresh, peppery radish. It reminds me of the late spring... my mother would slice up our fresh radishes and serve them on grainy bread with a little salt and pepper. Ah, those were the days... but I digress. Now, watch closely... / Radish Salad/萝卜沙拉！没有什么菜能够比得上一盘新鲜的胡椒萝卜。这让我想起来晚春的时候……我的母亲会将新鲜的萝卜切成片，然后撒上一点盐和胡椒粉，和全麦面包一起吃。啊，这些都是往事……我好像有点跑题了，仔细看好……",
        "12": "Artichoke Dip/Artichoke Dip! This is a delightful way to get more artichokes into your body. Personally, I don't even dip anything in there. I just guzzle the sauce down like it's a milkshake. Delicious. / Artichoke Dip/水煮洋蓟！这是让洋蓟的营养进入你体内的绝妙方式。我自己的话，就不会用什么东西蘸着吃。我只是像喝奶昔一样将这道菜大口吃下去。非常美味。",
        "10": "Trout Soup/Trout Soup! There's something about fresh-caught trout that just gets me buzzing. Maybe it's the subtle taste of the river. At any rate, I've got a wonderful trout soup recipe to share with you today... / Trout Soup/鳟鱼汤！这刚铺捉上来的鳟鱼不知为何让我有点小激动。也许是河鲜的鲜味刺激到我了。总之，我今天要和你们分享一种鳟鱼汤的绝妙烹饪法……",
        "14": "Chocolate Cake/Chocolate Cake! What better way to spend these cold winter nights than digging your way through a rich chocolate mountain? With my help, you'll be well on your way to creating the finest cake you've ever laid eyes on. Now, you're going to need a lot of sugar... / Chocolate Cake/巧克力蛋糕！在冬季的寒夜里，没有比品尝浓香的巧克力蛋糕更让人感到温暖的了吧？在我的帮助下，你很快就可以制作出最为精美的蛋糕。现在，你需要加入足够的糖……",
        "31": "Bruschetta/Bruschetta! It's a wonderfully simple appetizer that really showcases the quality of the ingredients. You'll need bread, tomato, and oil. First, you'll need to grill the bread. Slice the tomato and place onto the grilled bread. Then drizzle with oil and serve. I told you it was simple! / Bruschetta/意式烤面包！这是一道简单但非常美味的开胃菜，它真的能突显出原材料的质感。你需要准备的是面包、西红柿以及油。首先，将面包烤好。将西红柿切碎，并撒到烤好的面包上。然后，淋上一点油，就可以上桌了。我没骗你吧，做起来确实简单！",
        "7": "Maki Roll/Maki Roll! The delicate flavor of the ocean, sealed within a pillowy cloud of rice. Maybe a bit of wasabi for the adventurous. My mouth is watering as we speak. Oh, how I love sushi... / Maki Roll/生鱼片寿司！柔软的米饭将鱼的鲜味包裹其中。喜欢口味重点的，也可以来一点芥末。说着说着，我就开始流口水了。哦，我太喜欢寿司了……",
        "20": "Lucky Lunch/Lucky Lunch! An old legend has it that this meal is irresistible to spirits of luck and fortune. After consuming it, you're likely to attract a good spirit into your belly, where it will bless you with good fortune until the meal is digested! Sounds weird, huh? I can't say I believe it, but the meal is delicious nonetheless!  / Lucky Lunch/幸运午餐！在古老的传说中，这是一顿连幸运和财富之神都无法阻挡的午餐。你吃完之后，就会将幸运之气引入你的肚内，这股幸运之气会给你带来好运直到午餐全部被消化。听起来怪怪的，是吧？我不能说我一定相信，但是，不管如何，这午餐确实是美味啊！",
        "18": "Hashbrowns/Hashbrowns! This one's simple, but that's a good thing! You'll just want to shred some potatoes, add a liberal amount of salt, and fry to perfection in your favorite high-heat oil. Sounds easy, right? Well, I've got some pointers that'll make your job a lot easier...  / Hashbrowns/薯饼！这道菜看似简单，不过，真的是非常美味！先将土豆切成丝，然后撒上适量的盐，再用你最喜欢的热油将土豆丝炸好。感觉很简单，是吧？好吧，我可以给你们一些建议，让你们做起来更加简单……",
        "16": "Cranberry Candy/Cranberry Candy! Here's a fun one to help you celebrate the new year. Cranberries are quite bitter on their own, but submerge them in an ocean of sugar and they'll taste like angel's tears. Here's how you do it... / Cranberry Candy/蔓越莓糖果！这是一款你过新年时需要的绝妙糖果。蔓越莓本身就带有苦味，但是，把它们浸到大量的糖水中之后，尝起来简直就像是天使的眼泪。现在，看我怎么来做……",
        "22": "Maple Bar/Maple Bars! Ever notice how the maple bars are always first to disappear from the doughnut box? Perplexing, because your average maple bar tastes like a sweet hockey puck. Agree? Well, just wait until you try my recipe. You can really taste the forest in these bars. Okay, you're going to need real, quality maple syrup... / Maple Bar/枫糖棒！为什么枫糖棒总是第一个从甜甜圈盒中消失？令人费解吧，那是因为你们做的普通枫糖棒吃起来就像一个甜甜的冰球。同意吗？好吧，稍后就给你们展示我的配方。从这些派中，你真的能吃出森林的味道。好了，你所需要的就是一些正宗、上乘的枫糖浆……",
        "28": "Fiddlehead Risotto/Fiddlehead Risotto! Fiddlehead ferns are beautiful, but actually quite bland on their own. That's why you have to pay careful attention to the spices you add. I'll be honest, it's not very easy to make a good fiddlehead risotto. But with my help, you'll have the best chance at achieving it. / Fiddlehead Risotto/意式蕨菜炖饭！蕨菜看上去很漂亮，但是，直接吃的话，会感觉非常乏味。所以，你得多注意自己加入的香料。实话说，意式蕨菜炖饭要做好，还是非常难的。不过，在我的帮助下，你一定会成功做出一道美味的意式蕨菜炖饭。",
        "9": "Tortilla/Tortillas! How many of you are gnawing on a microwaved convenience-burrito while watching this program? Shame on you! You might as well wrap your beans in an old wash rag. Now, listen up. Once you've tried my fresh, rustic corn tortillas you'll never go back... / Tortilla/墨西哥薄饼！看这个节目的时候，有多少人还在咬着用微波炉烤出来的傻瓜式玉米煎饼呢？丢人啊。那样吃薄饼还不如直接把玉米粒裹到破旧的抹布里。现在，都给我听好了。如果你尝了我手工制作的新鲜玉米煎饼，你就再也不会像以前一样……",
        "29": "Poppyseed Muffin/Poppyseed Muffin! Poppies make beautiful ornamental flowers... but why not make full use of the plant with these delightful muffins? I'm a huge fan of poppy seeds. They're subtle, but they add a nice flavor and a great texture to bready desserts. And they're healthy! / Poppyseed Muffin/虞美人籽松糕！虞美人会开出非常迷人的花朵……但是，为什么不把虞美人和这可口的松饼充分融合到一起呢？我对虞美人籽情有独钟。这虞美人籽看起来没什么特别的，但是，它们会让面包甜点更具香味和质感。并且，它们还很健康！",
        "32": "Shrimp Cocktail/Shrimp Cocktail! Here's another good appetizer for you and your dinner guests. My cocktail sauce is extra zesty, and I'm sure you'll love it. Now, the first step...  / Shrimp Cocktail/鲜虾鸡尾酒！这是另一道会让你和你的客人非常喜欢的开胃菜。我制作的鸡尾酒汁极其鲜美，我相信你一定会爱上它的。好了，第一步是……",
        "23": "Pink Cake/A viewer from Pelican Town wrote to me recently... let's see... Her name's Haley. She wrote, 'I tried your pink cake last time I was in Zuzu City and I fell in love with it. Could you share the recipe on your next episode?'. Well, why not? It's a marvelous cake. And you'll never guess the secret ingredient... melon! / Pink Cake/有一位来自鹈鹕镇的观众最近写了一封信给我……我们来看看……她的名字是海莉。她写道：“上次我在祖祖市的时候，吃到了你做的粉色蛋糕，我马上就爱上它了。你能在下期节目中分享一下粉色蛋糕的配方吗？”。好吧，为什么不呢？这是一款非常棒的蛋糕。并且，你永远不会猜到其秘方是……甜瓜！",
        "26": "Blackberry Cobbler/Blackberry Cobbler! This one always reminds me of Stardew Valley. There's a few days in fall where the valley is overflowing with the most delicious blackberries I've ever tasted. If you can get your hands on some, I'd highly recommend them for this simple cobbler. / Blackberry Cobbler/黑莓脆皮饼！这道菜总会让我想起星露谷。秋季的那几天，星露谷到处都是我人生中吃过最美味的黑莓。如果你家里有一些这样的黑莓，我极力建议你将它们做成这简单黑莓脆皮饼。",
        "13": "Plum Pudding/Plum Pudding! Little Jack Horner is champing at the bit for this ooey-gooey delight. And who can blame him? The plums are floral and sweet, with just the right amount of tartness to fully activate every last one of your eager taste buds. You'll just have to try it and see for yourself... / Plum Pudding/葡萄干布丁！面对这种甜份充足的美食，小杰克霍纳已经显得迫不及待了。但谁会责怪他呢？这葡萄干真的是又香又甜，再加上适度的酸味，完全可以打开你沉睡中的味蕾。你真的需要亲身体验一下……",
        "15": "Pumpkin Pie/Pumpkin Pie! In my house, it's a tradition to eat pumpkin pie during the Feast of the Winter Star. The season just isn't complete without that wonderful flavor you can only achieve with the finest farm-fresh pumpkins. A little nutmeg, cinnamon, and clove will sweep you off to a land of crimson and gold...  / Pumpkin Pie/南瓜派！在我家里，冬日星盛宴的时候，会吃南瓜派，这已成一个习俗。如果你不吃上一口从农场采摘下来的新鲜、美味的南瓜，就会觉得这个季节总缺少了些什么。加上一点肉豆蔻、桂皮和丁香，你的眼前就会浮现出一片金红之地……",
        "4": "Omelet/Omelet! This is such a simple dish, but so often done incorrectly! A perfect omelet is a thing of beauty. It's a pure golden angel of gleaming egg, and I'm going to show you my secret method...  / Omelet/煎蛋卷！这是一道很简单的菜，但是，一不小心就会做坏。一个完美的煎蛋卷简直就是一件艺术品。这是一个纯金色、闪闪发光的天使之蛋，接下来，我要向你们展示一下我的绝技……",
        "27": "Crab Cakes/Crab Cakes! Crab meat is very flimsy on its own, but mixing it with bread crumbs and egg is a great way to give them some body. That's why these cakes are my favorite way to eat crab! But before you go cracking any shells, stay tuned for my essential seasoning mixture... / Crab Cakes/蟹黄糕！蟹肉本身就比较细腻，但是，将它与面包屑、鸡蛋搅拌混合之后，就变得非常入味了。这就是我喜欢吃蟹黄糕的原因。不过，在你敲碎蟹壳之前，先看一下我这个非常关键的调味料……",
        "25": "Fruit Salad/Fruit Salad! Here's a healthy and delicious treat to brighten up your day. The most important thing to remember is that you need ripe fruit. Forget the bland stuff they sell at the supermarket... I'm talking fresh-picked, juicy, bursting-with-flavor fruit. Okay, now watch closely... / Fruit Salad/水果沙拉！这是一道健康、美味的菜肴，可以让你每天都过得舒畅。最重要的就是要选取成熟的水果。可别给我提那些超市里卖的隔夜水果……我所说的是新鲜摘取的多汁、美味水果。好吧，现在仔细看好了……",
        "5": "Baked Fish/Baked Fish! Whenever I make this one at home, my two cats go bananas. I need a second chef around just to keep them from hopping on the counter for a bite! Just make sure the fish is fresh, preferably caught with your own rod! Now watch as I place the fish on a bed of spring greens... / Baked Fish/烤鱼！每当我在家做这道菜的时候，我那两只猫就会抓狂。我需要安排一位帮厨来看着它们，防止它们跳上来抢鱼吃。一定要选取新鲜的鱼，最好是你亲手钓的。好了，现在我要把鱼放到铺好的绿色蔬菜上……",
        "24": "Roasted Hazelnuts/Roasted Hazelnuts! I've got a nice old hazelnut tree behind my house, and every year I invite the family over for a nut roasting party! Once we start roasting, it's inevitable that the neighbors will show up. That rich, nutty smell is irresistible. Now, here's the family recipe...  / Roasted Hazelnuts/烤榛子！我的房子后面有一颗古老而漂亮的榛子树，每年，我都会邀请全家人过来举行一次果仁烧烤宴会！一旦我们开始烧烤，周围的邻居就会闻香而来。烤榛子的浓香真的是不可阻挡啊。好了，来看看我的家族秘方……",
        "17": "Pizza/Pizza! There's a reason pizza is a timeless culinary classic. You've got an artisan golden-brown crust, you've got a tangy, garlic-infused marinara sauce, and you're topping it all with a mouth-watering three-cheese blend. And we're just getting started! Let's throw some fresh pepper and tomato on the top. Oh, my! / Pizza/披萨！披萨是永恒的烹饪经典，这也是有其原因的。金黄色的精美饼胚已经出炉了，先浇一层蒜香浓郁的番茄酱，然后，再浇上一层让人口水直流的奶酪。这才刚刚开始！让我们在上面撒些新鲜胡椒和番茄。我的天！",
        "2": "Coleslaw/Coleslaw! Envisioning bland mounds of limp cabbage? You're not alone. But a great coleslaw can be so much more. Make sure you have juicy fresh cabbage for this one. Toss with a little vinegar and mayonnaise and you're all set. Ah, that's crisp. / Coleslaw/卷心菜沙拉！想吃上一大盘清淡而柔软的卷心菜？不光是你有这样的想法。其实卷心菜沙拉可以做得更加美味。做这道菜，一定要选取多汁、新鲜的卷心菜。撒上一点醋和沙拉酱就可以了。啊，非常脆爽。",
        "30": "Lobster Bisque/Lobster Bisque! You could serve this one to the governor himself. It's rich, creamy and delicious, with just the right amount of oceanic flavor. The hardest part is finding some lobster, but I'm sure you can do it. Heck, if you're feeling crafty you could catch one yourself with a crab pot! / Lobster Bisque/龙虾浓汤！你可以亲自将这道菜献给州长。这龙虾浓汤浓郁、奶香、美味，并且会让你感受到海洋的味道。要找到一些新鲜的龙虾是最难的，不过，我相信你可以做到的。好吧，如果你觉得自己够灵巧，那就亲自用蟹笼抓一只！",
        "8": "Bread/Bread! Breadmaking can be a very complex form of art, but I'll make it simple for you. The most important ingredient is flour, of course. But before we create the dough we'll need to activate our yeast. They prefer warm water and a little something to feed on. I use plain sugar, but honey or maple syrup will do!  / Bread/面包！制作面包可以说是一件非常复杂的事情，但是，我可以让它变得很简单。最重要的材料当然就是面粉了。不过，在和面之前，我们得让醒一下酵母。它们喜欢温水。我喜欢使用普通的糖，不过用蜂蜜或者枫糖浆也是可以的！",
        "6": "Pancakes/Pancakes! Sometimes I get carried away with fancy, complicated dishes... but there's something comforting about a simple pancake. You'll want plenty of butter and maple syrup to slather over these warm stacks... mmmm.... / Pancakes/薄煎饼！有的时候，我会被精致、复杂的菜肴吸引……不过，一块简单的薄煎饼也可以抚慰我的心灵。建议在这一层层热煎饼上涂上黄油和枫糖浆。"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/TV/TipChannel",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "74": "Winter's almost here. Make sure you're prepared to feed your animals hay over the winter, because they don't like going outside in the cold. Also, your grass won't keep growing after that first frost. Each silo can hold 240 pieces of hay, so make sure to do the math and figure out if you need to build any more! / 冬天马上来了。确保你已经为动物们准备了足量的干草，因为动物们冬天是不会外出觅食的。第一场寒潮来临之后，你的牧草就不会再生长了。每个筒仓可以储存 240 片干草，所以你要好好计算一下，看看需不需要额外建造更多的筒仓哦！",
        "106": "Ever see three little brown stems poking up out of the ground? They're hard to spot, sometimes. But if you dig on that spot, you'll always find something. Don't ask me how it works. / 你见过三根细小的棕色茎秆从地里冒出来吗？一般上很难发现。但你要是在该位置挖掘，就一定会找到些东西。不要问我个中原理。",
        "78": "Fish Focus: Walleye. You can find this fish on rainy evenings during the fall and winter. It can be found in any freshwater location. / 鱼类聚焦：鼓眼鱼。你可以在秋天和冬天的雨夜找到这种鱼。任何淡水水域都有它们的身影。",
        "221": "Folks, I've got an announcement to make. This is the last new episode of Livin' Off The Land before my retirement. I've had a good time, and I'll miss you folks. Oh, and I've been told the station's going to start playing reruns next year.  / 各位，我要宣布一件事情。我即将退休，这是最后一档离地生活节目。这段日子我过得很开心，我会想念你们的。哦，我已经告诉电视台，让他们明年开始进行重播。^^Take care! / ^照顾好自己！",
        "172": "Some farmers have reported strange things happening when large fields of cauliflower, melon, or pumpkin reach maturity. Hmmm. I can't verify it, myself. / 有农民汇报说，当大片的花椰菜、甜瓜或者南瓜成熟时，会发生一些奇怪的事情。嗯。我是无法证实了。",
        "137": "I'd like to talk about the famous Adventurer's Guild near Pelican Town. The guild leader, Marlon, has a nice rewards program for anyone brave enough to slay monsters in the local caves. Adventurers will receive powerful items in exchange for slaying large quantities of monsters. There's a poster on the wall with more details. Very cool! / 鹈鹕镇附近有个著名的冒险者公会。会长马龙制定了一个奖励计划来激励勇士前往当地的山洞中击杀怪物。冒险者杀死大量怪物之后，可以获得相应的强大道具。墙上张贴了海报，里面写了相关的详细信息。加油吧！",
        "36": "Let's talk corn. It's an unusual crop because it lasts for two seasons! That's right, while most crops die when the season changes, corn lives on. You can grow it in both summer and fall. Now, get out there and plant some corn! / 我们来说说玉米吧。这是一种非同寻常的农作物，因为它可以生长两季。没错，季节变迁的时候，很多农作物都会枯萎，但是玉米却能够继续生长。你可以在夏季和秋季种植玉米。那就快去行动起来，去种一些玉米吧！",
        "186": "Fish Focus: Albacore. This fish can be found either early in the morning or at night. Look for it in the ocean in fall or winter. / 鱼类聚焦：青花鱼。这种鱼可以在清早或者晚上找到。在秋天或者冬天的大海中寻找它吧。",
        "67": "Fish Focus: Salmon. Salmon return to their spawning ground in fall to lay eggs. That means the rivers are chock-full of them! You can only find them in fall, so get out there and cast your pole. / 鱼类聚焦：鲑鱼。秋天，鲑鱼会回到它们的产卵地进行产卵。所以河流里面会充斥着鲑鱼！只有秋天才会有垂钓到鲑鱼的机会，所以好好把握这个机遇吧。",
        "29": "Summer's here, along with a whole slew of new crops to plant! Take hops, for example. The vines take a while to grow, but once they're mature they can be harvested every day. Good luck! / 夏天来了，可以种植各种各样新的农作物了！就拿啤酒花来说吧。它的藤蔓成长起来需要一段时间，一旦长成，就每天都会结出丰硕的果实。所以祝你好运吧！",
        "53": "Fall's almost here! It's arguably the most lucrative season for farmers, so make sure you're saving some money to buy new seeds. If you haven't upgraded your watering can by now, it's probably a good idea. / 秋天就快到了！毋庸置疑，秋天对于农民来说，是一个丰收的季节，所以，一定要存下一些钱来买新的种子哦。如果你还没更换过喷壶，那现在是一个好时机。",
        "15": "It's salmonberry season! All across the countryside, bushes are teeming with juicy little berries, and they're free for the taking! Harvesting them is a great way to earn some extra cash. / 美莓成熟的季节到了！整个乡村的草丛中都布满了小巧而多汁的美莓，你可以随意采摘！把它们采摘下来出售，就可以挣到一笔额外的收入。",
        "141": "I've heard that some folks stand near moving trains to gather any debris that falls off. Wow... the things people will do for a freebie! / 听说有些人会守候在移动的火车旁以拾取车上掉下来的物品。啧啧……这年头的人为了免费物品真是什么事都干得出来！",
        "57": "Let's talk sunflowers. When you harvest them you'll not only get a nice flower, but you'll likely get some seeds as well. You can replant those seeds or sell them. I'm sold! / 我们来说说向日葵吧。当你收割向日葵的时候，你不仅获得漂亮的花朵，还可以获得一些种子。你可以再次种下这些种子或拿去卖。想想就有点小激动！",
        "162": "Item Spotlight: Keg. The classic use of a keg is to make wine out of grapes. But did you know you can make wine out of any fruit? Yep. / 道具聚焦：酒桶。酒桶的经典用途就是制作葡萄酒。但是，你是否知道任何水果都可以做成酒？对啊。^You can also make juice out of veggies. / 你还可以把蔬菜做成果汁呢。",
        "64": "It's blackberry season! Bushes across the countryside are overflowing with ripe fruit. Just go outside and see for yourself! / 黑莓成熟的季节到了！乡村的所有草丛中都布满了成熟的果实。你可以出去自己看看！",
        "190": "Fish Focus: Woodskip, sandfish, and scorpion carp. The woodskip is said to only live deep in the woods. The sandfish and scorpion carp can only be found in desert oases. / 鱼类聚焦：林跃鱼、沙鱼以及蝎鲤。据说，林跃鱼只生存在丛林深处。沙鱼和蝎鲤只能在沙漠绿洲中找到。",
        "50": "Most towns have a seasonal calendar in front of the general store. It's a good idea to check on that now and then to get a feel for what's going on in the community. Make sure to check for any job postings as well! / 大多数小镇上的杂货店门口都张贴了季节历。时而看一下季节历，确实不错的，你可以了解到社区里的一些时事。同时，一定要看一下有么有招聘广告！",
        "11": "Woes from crows? Sounds like you need a scarecrow! Placing a scarecrow on your farm deters crows from a pretty good distance. Make sure you protect your valuable crops! / 乌鸦会来捣乱？看来你需要一个稻草人！在你的农场设置一个稻草人，可以把乌鸦吓退到百里之外。一定要保护好珍贵的庄稼！^One more thing... need a bigger backpack to hold all your stuff? Check your local general store. / 还有一件事……你如果需要更大空间的背包来装道具的话，可以到当地的杂货店去看看。",
        "179": "Looking to get married? You're going to need a Mermaid's Pendant. Everyone this side of the Gem Sea knows what it means when you give them a Mermaid's Pendant. / 想结婚？那你就需要一个美人鱼吊坠。宝石海这边的每个人都知道赠送美人鱼吊坠代表什么意思。^Getting your hands on such a pendant can be tricky. Every region seems to have their own custom, but it always has something to do with the beach or ocean. / 当你收到这样的吊坠时，情况就比较微妙了。每个地区好像都有自己的习俗，不过，这些习俗基本上都是和海滩或海洋有关系。",
        "18": "Ah, refreshing rain... a Farmer's best friend! When it rains, you don't have to water your crops. Use this to your advantage! / 啊，清爽的雨……这是农民的最好朋友！下雨时，你就不用亲自去浇灌庄稼了。要充分利用这种天赐良机！",
        "22": "Get your hands on a fishin' pole and sell your catch! Fishing is a great way to make a little extra cash when you have some down time. The distance your bobber lands from any dry land determines what kinds of fish you'll hook... as well as the location, season, time of day, and weather! / 甩出你的鱼竿去钓条大肥鱼，钓到的鱼可以拿去卖！较闲时钓鱼可以挣取额外收入。鱼钩抛离陆地的距离决定了你能钓到什么样的鱼……其他影响因素还有地点、季节、时间、以及天气！",
        "81": "Winter's coming soon... and that means your farming operations will be coming to a halt. No crops grow in winter, unless you're lucky enough to have a greenhouse. But there's still plenty to do! More next time. / 冬天马上就要来了……这就意味着你的农活可以告一段落了。冬天里，没有庄稼可以生长，除非你建造了温室。不过，你还是可以忙其他的事的！来年的冬天你会更忙碌。",
        "204": "If you have adult barn animals, and space left in your barn... there's always a chance one of your animals could give birth. It's something to keep in mind. / 如果你的畜棚中有成年动物，并且畜棚还有空间……那么它们就有几率产子。",
        "85": "Winter... A time when all the world goes quiet.  Now's a great time to do some mining, fishing and gathering. Upgrade your tools in preparation for a productive spring. Or get your local carpenter to build something on your farm! Stock up on resources, upgrade, and prepare for the next year. / 冬天……这是整个世界都会安静下来的季节。现在是采矿、钓鱼以及聚会的大好时机。更换你的工具，为春天的耕种做好准备。或者，让当地的木匠为你的农场打造些木具。储备资源、更换工具，为来年做好充分的准备。",
        "120": "Got a kitchen? Cooking is a great way to enhance your abilities. Not only do they provide a convenient source of energy, but many dishes temporarily increase your skills, speed, and more! Smells good, don't it? / 有厨房吗？烹饪是提升能力的绝佳方式。很多菜肴不仅会赋予你能量，而且还可以临时提升你的技能、速度以及其它能力。是不是想想就有点小激动？",
        "214": "Underneath all that snow, spring seeds are champing at the bit to start their new lives in the sun. Don't be surprised when spring rolls around and your farm needs some tidying up! / 在层层积雪下方，春天的种子正在崭露头角，准备在阳光中绽放自己全新的生命。当春天再度来临的时候，你别太惊讶于农场的“惨状”，只要下点功夫清理一番就好了！",
        "95": "There's a couple fish you can only find in winter... Squid and Lingcod. Squid can be caught from the ocean in the evening. Lingcod can be found in fresh water all day. Of course, there's rumors of extremely rare and unique fish that can only be found in particular seasons, but I don't have any information on them. / 下面这些鱼，你只有在冬天才能找到：墨鱼和蛇鳕鱼。墨鱼可以在夜晚的大海中抓到。蛇鳕鱼则出现在淡水湖中。当然，也有传言说还有一些非常稀有和奇特的鱼，只有在特别的季节中才会出现。但是我没有它们的相关资料。",
        "169": "If you managed to get your hands on a 'rare seed', now's the time to plant it. Although it's said to take all season to grow, reliable sources have told me it actually takes just 24 days. The end result is rumored to be the sweetest fruit in the entire world. / 如果你得到了“稀有种子”，现在就该把它种下了。传言说这种子需要一个季节来生长，但是，我已得到确切信息，实际上只要 24 天。传说它长成之后会结出全世界最甜的果子。",
        "116": "Fish Focus: Eel. Eels can be caught from the ocean in the spring and fall, during rainy evenings. / 鱼类聚焦：鳗鱼。鳗鱼可以在春天和秋天的雨夜从大海中抓到。",
        "134": "Here's a tip for you adventurers out there... don't forget your weapon's special attack! Swords can block incoming attacks, which is very useful when slimes are jumping at you. Clubs can pound the ground, sending enemies flying... and with a dagger you can perform a super-quick triple-strike attack! Be safe. / 对于冒险者，我有个提示……不要忘记武器的特别攻击！宝剑可阻挡敌人的攻击，对付史莱姆很有用。棍棒可以敲击地面以震飞敌人……匕首可以用来施展瞬间三连击！出外行走要注意安全哦。",
        "99": "Let's talk geodes. Geodes are hollow stones that often contain valuable minerals. A blacksmith can crack them open for you for a fee. Now, there's different kinds of geodes... and each one yields a different subset of minerals. The rare \"omni-geode\", however, can contain every kind of mineral. / 我们来说说晶球吧。晶球是中空的石头，通常含有珍贵的矿物。只需一点辛劳费，铁匠就可以帮你敲开它们。晶球也有很多种类，每种晶球都含有不同的矿物。不过，稀有的“混合晶球”则会含有所有种类的矿物。",
        "46": "Summer's known for its lightning storms. If you know how to craft a lightning rod, you can harvest the electricity and create battery packs. These can be sold or used for crafting! / 夏天肯定出现闪电风暴。如果你知道如何制作避雷针，那么你可以收集闪电来制作电池。这些电池可以出售或者用于加工其他物品！",
        "71": "Got any tappers? Crafty foragers known how to build 'em. You can attach them to the wild trees that grow all over. Maple trees yield maple syrup, oak trees provide resin, and pine trees produce pine tar. Syrup's the most valuable but all tree products have their uses! / 有树液采集器吗？聪明的采集者知道如何使用它们。你可以把它们固定到野生树上。枫树会流出枫糖浆，橡树会出树脂，松树会流出松焦油。糖浆是最珍贵的，不过，所有树上的产物都有其用途！",
        "151": "Fish Focus: Super Cucumber. You can find this rare fish in the ocean. It only comes out in the evening, during summer and fall. / 鱼类聚焦：超级海参。你可以在大海中找到这种珍贵的鱼。它只会在夏天和秋天的晚上出现。",
        "165": "Do you have a journal? Don't forget to check it from time to time. It's easy to forget that you've written something important down. / 你手头上有日志不？别忘了时常查看一下自己的日志。你容易忘记的重要信息都记录在里面了。",
        "32": "Here's a rundown of the fish you can only find in summer: Dorado, found in forest rivers during the day. Rainbow Trout, found in forest rivers and in the mountains during the day. Pufferfish, found in the ocean in the early afternoon. And Octopus, found in the ocean during the morning. Catch them while you can! / 下面这些鱼，你只有在夏天才能找到：麻哈脂鲤，可以在白天的森林河流中找到。虹鳟鱼，可以在白天的森林河流和山涧找到。河豚，可以下午时分的大海中找到。还有章鱼，可以在早晨的大海中找到。可以的话，就抓住它们！",
        "127": "It's salmonberry season! All across the countryside, bushes are teeming with juicy little berries, and they're free for the taking! Harvesting them is a great way to earn some extra cash. / 美莓成熟的季节到了！整个乡村的草丛中都布满了小巧而多汁的美莓，你可以随意采摘！把它们采摘下来出售，就可以挣到一笔额外的收入。",
        "148": "Here's a reminder of the fish you can only find in summer: Dorado, found in forest rivers during the day. Rainbow Trout, found in forest rivers and in the mountains during the day. Pufferfish, found in the ocean in the early afternoon. And Octopus, found in the ocean during the morning. Catch them while you can! / 再次提醒一下，下面这些鱼，你只有在夏天才能找到：剑鱼，可以在白天的森林可流中找到。虹鳟鱼，可以在白天的森林河流和山涧找到。河豚鱼，可以下午时分的大海中找到。还有章鱼，可以在早晨的大海中找到。可以的话，就抓住它们！",
        "4": "This one's for you folks living in Stardew Valley. Check for spring onion southwest of town, where the river meets the ocean. You can sometimes find a whole bunch growing right out of the dirt. / 给星露谷的居民一个提示。去查看下生长在小镇西南部的野葱，小镇的西南方是河川与大海交汇的地方。偶尔能找到一簇簇的野葱从泥土中冒出来。",
        "25": "Fruit trees. They take an entire season to grow, so plan ahead! If the area directly surrounding your new tree isn't clear, it will interfere with growth. Once your fruit tree is mature, it'll produce delicious fruit for you every day while in season. Better start savin' up! / 果树。它们需要一个季节的时间来生长，所以，要提前种下！如果你新种下的果树周围没除草干净，果树的生长就会受到影响。当你的果树长成之后，只要是在成熟的季节，它就会每天为你结出可口的果子。你该开始谋划了！",
        "43": "Got a spa in your town? Relax and hold still in the steaming hot water to replenish your energy. Ahh... feels good, don't it? / 要在镇上做一次大保健吗？静静地躺在冒着热气的泉水中，放松自己，补充能量。啊……那画面实在太美丽，对吧？",
        "102": "If you really want to make someone happy, give them their favorite gift on their birthday! Trust me. / 如果你想让某些人开心，你就得在他们生日的时候送上他们最喜欢的礼物！信我没错。",
        "211": "Item Spotlight: Worm Bin. Need an endless supply of bait? Build yourself a worm bin. Once you've got one going, you'll get a few pieces of bait every single day. / 道具聚焦：虫箱。需要源源不断的诱饵？自己制作一个虫箱吧。只要把虫箱运作起来，那每天都能收获到一些诱饵。",
        "60": "If you're a farmer in a small town, it's likely you'll be invited to create a \"grange display\" at some point. Typically, a grange display consists of 9 items that best showcase your talents. Shoot for high quality, high value items and make sure to have a variety as well. Fish, minerals, artisan goods, fruit, and vegetables are all good to have! / 如果你是一位小镇上的农民，那么，你迟早会被邀请去举办一场所谓的“农庄展”。具体来说，你需要展示 9 件最能突出你的才能的物品。尽量挑选出高质量、高价值的物品，而且种类一定要丰富。鱼、矿石、手工艺品、水果以及蔬菜都适合出展！",
        "8": "Let's talk fences. Fences are useful for keeping weeds at bay and protecting your crops. They also let farmers contain their livestock. Fences break down after a while, but stone, iron, and hardwood fences last a lot longer than basic wood! / 接下来就说说篱笆吧。篱笆有助于抑制杂草的蔓延和保护你的庄稼。篱笆还可以让农民圈养他们的牲口。一般的木篱笆很快就会破损，但是石头、铁以及硬木做的篱笆可以用很久！",
        "1": "This one's for all you greenhorns out there: chop wood and search for wild forage to earn some cash while waiting on your first harvest! / 给所有新人一个提示：在等待第一次收成的同时，你可以去砍柴和收集野生牧草以挣取些额外收入！",
        "109": "Ever had the urge to dig around in your neighbor's trash? Ew! Hey, if that's your thing, just don't do it when anyone's around. If they notice you, they'll be seriously grossed out, and it'll harm your friendship. Well, unless they're into the same thing. / 是否很想挖一挖你邻居的垃圾堆？嘿，如果你真有这种奇葩想法，那就确保在没有人看见的时候才去挖。如果被人发现，那就会恶心到邻居，影响邻里之间的友谊。除非对方跟你一样奇葩。",
        "123": "Item Spotlight: Crab Pot. Experienced anglers know how to craft crab pots. Despite the name, the pots can be used to catch a wide variety of aquatic critters, in both fresh and salt water. Just place your crab pot in the water and load with bait. Come back the next day and check on it to see what you caught. You'll need to load it with bait again to catch more. / 道具聚焦：蟹笼。经验丰富的垂钓者都懂得如何制作蟹笼。除了抓螃蟹外，蟹笼还可以用来抓取淡水湖和咸水湖中的各种水生生物。只要将蟹笼放入水中，并装入诱饵。第二天再回来，看看蟹笼中有没有捕获什么东西。如果想继续使用，那就得重新装入诱饵。",
        "176": "It's blackberry season! Bushes across the countryside are overflowing with ripe fruit. Just go outside and see for yourself! / 黑莓成熟的季节到了！乡村的所有草丛中都布满了成熟的果实。你可以出去自己看看！",
        "39": "Starting tomorrow, an unusual amount of shells and corals are expected to wash up on beaches all around the world. I'm no scientist, but I've heard it's something to do with crab mating season. At any rate, you could make some good coin combing your local beach. / 从明天开始，大量的贝壳和珊瑚会被冲到全世界的海滩上。我不是一位科学家，但是，我听说这和螃蟹的交配季节有关系。不管怎么样，你可以利用当地的海滩挣一笔大钱。",
        "130": "Let's talk honey. No, not you, silly. I'm talking about the sweet product made by our friends, the bees. Here's the thing... if you've got some flowers blooming near your beehouse your bees can produce flavored honey. Otherwise you'll only get 'wild honey'. Pretty sweet, huh? / 我们来说说蜂蜜吧。顾名思义，蜂蜜就是蜜蜂产出的蜜糖。如果你的蜂房附近有鲜花开放，那么，你的蜜蜂会产出美味的蜂蜜。否则，你只能收获到“野蜂蜜”。厉害吧？",
        "218": "If you've got your hands on a gold pan, keep an eye out for something sparkly in the water. / 如果你有一个淘金盘，那一定要多留意水中是否有发光耀眼的东西。^There's often good ore in there, free for the taking!    / 水中经常会有珍贵的矿石出现，免费的哦！",
        "207": "Fish Focus: Catfish. This relatively rare fish comes out of hiding when it rains. You'll find them living in rivers beside towns, where they enjoy feeding on whatever scraps end up in the water. They don't like hot weather, so don't bother fishing for them in the summer! / 鱼类聚焦：鲶鱼。这是一种比较罕见的鱼，下雨时会出现。你会发现它们生存在小镇旁的河流中，以掉到水中的残羹剩饭为食。它们不喜欢炎热的天气，所以，在夏天时就别煞费苦心来钓它们了！",
        "113": "Well, a new year has arrived. Keep your eyes peeled for any new kinds of seeds being stocked in your local general store. Hopefully you upgraded your tools during the winter and you're ready for a productive year! / 新年到了。好好留意一下当地杂货店中有没有什么新型种子。希望你已经在冬天时更换过工具，为新的一年做好了准备！",
        "193": "It's just a couple days until communities around the Ferngill Republic celebrate Spirit's Eve! One tradition you may not know of is the search for the golden pumpkin. If your town has a haunted maze, then you can be sure there's a golden pumpkin hidden somewhere. Those things are valuable! / 再过几天，芬吉尔共和国一带就要迎来万灵节了！你也许不知道有这么一个习俗：寻找黄金南瓜。如果你的镇上有个闹鬼迷宫，那么里面肯定藏有黄金南瓜。找到就能卖大钱哦！",
        "183": "Item Spotlight: Recycling Machine. Have you been catching a lot of junk while fishing? It's all too common in this day and age. Well, with a recycling machine you can turn those items into something useful. Just place your trash items into the machine and let it do its thing. Each type of trash produces different kinds of items. / 道具聚焦：回收机。你在钓鱼的时候是否钓到过很多垃圾？在这个时代，已经不足为奇了。好吧，有了回收机，你就可以将这些垃圾转变成有用的东西。只要将你的垃圾放入回收机内，让它自行工作就行了。不同类型的垃圾可以转化成不同种类的物品",
        "92": "Find any tree seeds while chopping wood? You can plant those in the ground and a new tree will grow. Get creative! / 砍柴时找到了一些树木的种子？你可以将种子种到地里，这样，一棵新的树就会长出来了。发挥你的创造性吧！",
        "158": "Here's an idea... start a wild tree orchard! Put tappers on those trees and harvest the valuable syrup. Or don't! See if I care. / 我想到一个主意……建一个野生果园！将树液采集器固定到这些树上，然后收集珍贵的糖浆。你不照做也没事！我毫不在乎。",
        "88": "Wondering how to get your hands on 'Refined Quartz'? Just put a regular old quartz in the furnace. You'll need a lump of coal to fuel the fire. / 想知道怎样才可以获得“精制石英”吗？你须要将一块普通的旧石英放入炉内。然后用一些煤炭来起火。",
        "200": "Item Spotlight: Crystalarium. This amazing machine can create infinite copies of any kind of gemstone. Just place the gemstone you'd like to copy in the machine let it do its thing. It might take a while, but hey... that's pure profit! / 道具聚焦：宝石复制机。这一款神奇的机器可以无限制地复制各种宝石。只要将你想要复制的宝石放入机器内，让机器自行工作，过一段时间后，嘿嘿……财源滚滚来！",
        "197": "Folks, take my advice. You're going to need a nursery in your house before you can have kids. Baby needs a crib! / 各位，请听我一言。在你有小孩之前，务必先在家中建一个育儿室。小宝宝需要一张婴儿床！",
        "144": "Animal Spotlight: Pig. / 动物聚焦：猪。^^In these parts, pigs are trained to sniff out valuable truffles. You've got to let the porkers outside and be patient... they'll work their magic when they're good and ready. Make oil out of the truffles to maximize your profit. / ^这一带的猪都受过专业训练，可以嗅找珍贵的松露。你只要放这些猪出去自由行动，然后耐心地等待就行了。收获到的松露可以加工做成油来卖。",
        "155": "I know it's hard... but stop worrying so much about your horse! You can leave them anywhere and they'll make their way back home. They're very smart and independent animals! / 我知道这很难……但是，你真的不用担心自己的马儿！你可以把它们扔在任何地方，它们自己能够找到回家的路。马是一种非常聪明和独立的动物！"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Objects",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Fields": {
        "558": {
          "DisplayName": "Thunder Egg / 雷公蛋",
          "Description": "According to legend, angry thunder spirits would throw these stones at one another. / 根据传说，愤怒的雷霆神灵会朝彼此扔这些石头。"
        },
        "816": {
          "DisplayName": "Fossil Stone / Fossil Stone",
          "Description": "Break apart to obtain fossils and bones. / Break apart to obtain fossils and bones."
        },
        "247": {
          "DisplayName": "Oil / 油",
          "Description": "All purpose cooking oil. / 可煎可炸的万用食用油。"
        },
        "532": {
          "DisplayName": "Jade Ring / 翡翠戒指",
          "Description": "Increases critical strike power by 10%. / 增加 10% 的致命一击能量。"
        },
        "324": {
          "DisplayName": "Iron Fence / 铁围栏",
          "Description": "Lasts longer than a stone fence. / 比石围栏更耐用。"
        },
        "434": {
          "DisplayName": "Stardrop / 星之果实",
          "Description": "A mysterious fruit that empowers those who eat it. The flavor is like a dream... a powerful personal experience, yet difficult to describe to others. / 一种神秘莫测的水果，给予食用者力量。它有梦幻般的味道……给人留下十分强烈的回忆，然而只可意会不可言传。"
        },
        "Powdermelon": {
          "DisplayName": "Powdermelon / 霜瓜",
          "Description": "Named for the powdery coating that forms on the surface, this melon is crisp and sweet, with a delicate flavor. / 因表面结一层白霜而得名，瓜肉鲜脆清甜。"
        },
        "748": {
          "DisplayName": "Rotten Plant / 腐烂的植物",
          "Description": "Decomposing organic material. It's slimy and unpleasant. / 分解有机物质。黏稠且还不好闻。"
        },
        "441": {
          "DisplayName": "Explosive Ammo / 爆炸弹丸",
          "Description": "Fire this with the slingshot. / 可以用弹弓进行发射。"
        },
        "137": {
          "DisplayName": "Smallmouth Bass / 小嘴鲈鱼",
          "Description": "A freshwater fish that is very sensitive to pollution. / 一种对污染很敏感的淡水鱼。"
        },
        "68": {
          "DisplayName": "Topaz / 黄水晶",
          "Description": "Fairly common but still prized for its beauty. / 很常见，但是因为漂亮还是很有价值。"
        },
        "156": {
          "DisplayName": "Ghostfish / 鬼鱼",
          "Description": "A pale, blind fish found in underground lakes. / 一种在地下湖里能找到的苍白色的盲鱼。"
        },
        "863": {
          "DisplayName": "Phoenix Ring / 凤凰戒指",
          "Description": "Once a day, regain some health after being knocked out in combat. / 在战斗中被击倒后恢复些许生命值，一天仅限一次。"
        },
        "560": {
          "DisplayName": "Ocean Stone / 海洋石",
          "Description": "An old legend claims these stones are the mosaics of ancient mermaids. / 古老的传说声称这些石头是远古美人鱼的镶嵌画。"
        },
        "186": {
          "DisplayName": "Large Milk / 大壶牛奶",
          "Description": "A large jug of cow's milk. / 一大壶牛奶。"
        },
        "16": {
          "DisplayName": "Wild Horseradish / 野山葵",
          "Description": "A spicy root found in the spring. / 春天生长的一种根茎香料。"
        },
        "143": {
          "DisplayName": "Catfish / 鲶鱼",
          "Description": "An uncommon fish found in streams. / 一种能在小溪里找到的罕见鱼类。"
        },
        "822": {
          "DisplayName": "Fossilized Tail / 尾巴化石",
          "Description": "This tail has a club-like feature at the tip. / 这条尾巴的尖端像棍子。"
        },
        "111": {
          "DisplayName": "Rusty Spur / 生锈的靴刺",
          "Description": "An old spur that was once attached to a cowboy's boot. People must have been raising animals in this area for many generations. / 曾经连在某个牛仔靴子上的旧靴刺。肯定已经有好几代的人在此饲养动物了。"
        },
        "551": {
          "DisplayName": "Lunarite / 酸性月岩",
          "Description": "The cratered white orbs form a tight cluster. / 这些坑坑洼洼的矿石会紧密的聚集在一起。"
        },
        "159": {
          "DisplayName": "Crimsonfish / 绯红鱼",
          "Description": "Lives deep in the ocean but likes to lay its eggs in the warm summer water. / 它住在深海里但是喜欢在温暖的夏天产卵。"
        },
        "79": {
          "DisplayName": "Secret Note / 秘密纸条",
