        },
        "710": {
          "DisplayName": "Crab Pot / 蟹笼",
          "Description": "Place it in the water, load it with bait, and check the next day to see if you've caught anything. Works in streams, lakes, and the ocean. / 放在水中，装上诱饵，隔一天再检查有没有抓到东西。可以在溪流、湖泊和大海使用。"
