          "Description": "A broken branch. Chop with an axe to obtain wood. / A broken branch. Chop with an axe to obtain wood."
        },
        "293": {
          "DisplayName": "Brick Floor / 红砖地板",
          "Description": "Place on the ground to create paths or to decorate your floors. / 放在地上修建小路，也可以装饰地板。"
        },
        "835": {
          "DisplayName": "Mango Sapling / 芒果幼苗",
          "Description": "Takes 28 days to produce a mature Mango tree. Bears fruit in the summer, or all year round when planted on Ginger Island. / 28 天成熟为芒果树。夏季结果实；种在姜岛上，一年四季都会结果实。"
