        },
        "556": {
          "DisplayName": "Orpiment / 雌黄",
          "Description": "Despite its high toxicity, this Mineral is widely used in manufacturing and folk medicine. / 尽管它毒性很强，它还是有广泛的加工以及制药用途。"
        },
        "167": {
