        "593": {
          "DisplayName": "Summer Spangle / 夏季亮片",
          "Description": "A tropical bloom that thrives in the humid summer air. Has a sweet, tangy aroma. / 一种热带花朵，生长于潮湿的夏日季节。拥有芬香刺鼻的味道。"
        },
        "681": {
          "DisplayName": "Rain Totem / 雨水图腾",
          "Description": "Activate to greatly increase the chance for rain tomorrow. Consumed on use. / 激活后，大大增加明天下雨的概率。消耗品。"
