          "Description": "Full of antioxidants. / 充满了抗氧化物。"
        },
        "PetLicense": {
          "DisplayName": "Pet License / 宠物饲养证",
          "Description": "Invite a new pet into your home. If you don't have enough outdoor pet bowls for your pets, they will become upset. / 邀请一只新宠物到你家。如果室外的宠物碗数量不够，宠物会不高兴。"
        },
        "386": {
          "DisplayName": "Iridium Ore / 铱矿石",
