          "Description": "Give this to the person you want to marry. / 把它送给你未来的伴侣。"
        },
        "885": {
          "DisplayName": "Fiber Seeds / 纤维种子",
          "Description": "Plant these in any season. Does not require watering. Harvest with the scythe. Takes 7 days to grow. / 所有季节都可以种植。不需要浇水。用镰刀收割。7 天长成。"
        },
        "270": {
          "DisplayName": "Corn / 玉米",
          "Description": "One of the most popular grains. The sweet, fresh cobs are a summer favorite. / 最常见的庄稼之一。甜甜的新鲜玉米棒是夏天最好的小吃。"
        },
        "288": {
          "DisplayName": "Mega Bomb / 超级炸弹",
