        "122": {
          "DisplayName": "Dwarf Gadget / 矮人小工具",
          "Description": "It's a piece of the advanced technology once known to the dwarves. It's still glowing and humming, but you're unable to understand how it works. / 这个小工具是矮人先进工艺的一小块结晶。它还在发光和响动，但是你无法理解它的工作原理。"
