          "Description": "A well preserved cog that must have been part of some ancient machine. This could be dwarven technology. / 一个保存完好的齿轮，它一定是某个古代机器的一部分。这可能是矮人工艺出品。"
        },
        "371": {
          "DisplayName": "Quality Retaining Soil / 高级保湿土壤",
          "Description": "This soil has a good chance of staying watered overnight. Mix into tilled soil. / 这种土壤有很大几率隔夜依然保持湿润。使用时加到犁过的土地中。"
        },
        "378": {
          "DisplayName": "Copper Ore / 铜矿石",
          "Description": "A common ore that can be smelted into bars. / 一种常见的矿石，能被熔炼成铜锭。"
        },
        "Book_Woodcutting": {
          "DisplayName": "Woody's Secret / 伐木秘事",
          "Description": "Felled trees have a 5% chance to yield double the wood. / 砍倒的树有 5% 的几率掉落双倍木头。"
        },
        "121": {
          "DisplayName": "Dwarvish Helm / 矮人头盔",
          "Description": "It's one of the helmets commonly worn by dwarves. The thick metal plating protects them from falling debris and stalactites. / 这是矮人常戴的头盔之一。厚厚的金属镀层能保护他们不受落石伤害。"
        },
        "909": {
          "DisplayName": "Radioactive Ore / 放射性矿石",
          "Description": "It's glowing with dangerous energy... Can be smelted into bars. / 它散发出危险的能量……可以熔炼成矿锭。"
        },
        "PrizeTicket": {
          "DisplayName": "Prize Ticket / 兑奖券",
          "Description": "Bring this to the prize machine in Lewis' house for a special reward. / 在刘易斯家的兑奖机领取特殊奖励。"
        },
        "90": {
          "DisplayName": "Cactus Fruit / 仙人掌果子",
          "Description": "The sweet fruit of the prickly pear cactus. / 尖刺仙人掌的甜美果实。"
