          "Description": "Break apart to obtain amethysts. / Break apart to obtain amethysts."
        },
        "704": {
          "DisplayName": "Dorado / 麻哈脂鲤",
          "Description": "A fierce carnivore with brilliant orange scales. / 凶猛的肉食鱼，有着绚烂的橙色鳞片。"
