        "ChallengeBait": {
          "DisplayName": "Challenge Bait / 挑战鱼饵",
          "Description": "A \"perfect\" catch yields triple the fish. However, each time a fish escapes the \"fishing bar\", the catch is reduced. / “完美”钓鱼时可获得三条鱼。鱼每逃离“钓鱼条”一次，产量就减少一条。"
