          "Description": "Use to gather ore from streams. Has bigger and better yields than a copper pan. It also has a small chance to immediately cause another panning spot to appear. / 可以收集河流中的矿石，产出的矿石比铜淘盘更多、品质更好。有小概率立即引出另一个淘金地点。"
