      "Fields": {
        "1": {
          "DisplayName": "Shorts / 短裤",
          "Description": "Perfect for a hot summer's day... your legs will thank you. / 炎炎夏日的绝配……你的腿会很感激。"
        },
        "9": {
          "DisplayName": "Tight Pants / 紧身裤",
          "Description": "A very tight pair of pants. / 很紧的裤子。"
        },
        "998": {
          "DisplayName": "Prismatic Pants / 五彩裤子",
          "Description": "Pants that shimmer with prismatic energy. / 有五彩能量而微微发光的裤子。"
        },
        "13": {
          "DisplayName": "Relaxed Fit Shorts / 休闲短裤",
          "Description": "These shorts have a little more room for the legs. / 这条短裤给腿留出了更多空间。"
        },
        "15": {
          "DisplayName": "Trimmed Lucky Purple Shorts / 镶边幸运紫色短裤",
          "Description": "Purple silk shorts trimmed in luxurious gold... / 镶了金边的紫色丝织短裤……"
        },
        "11": {
          "DisplayName": "Simple Dress / 简单长裙",
          "Description": "A soft, smooth, medium length dress. / 柔软光滑、中等长度的裙子。"
        },
        "999": {
          "DisplayName": "Prismatic Genie Pants / 五彩神怪裤",
          "Description": "Pants that shimmer with prismatic energy. / 有五彩能量而微微发光的裤子。"
        },
        "4": {
          "DisplayName": "Pleated Skirt / 褶裙",
          "Description": "A cute pleated skirt. / 漂亮的褶裙。"
        },
        "3": {
          "DisplayName": "Skirt / 短裙",
          "Description": "A cute skirt. / 漂亮的裙子。"
        },
        "5": {
          "DisplayName": "Dinosaur Pants / 恐龙裤",
          "Description": "These pants were thought to have gone extinct a long time ago! / 大家都以为这种裤子很久以前就灭绝了！"
        },
        "12": {
          "DisplayName": "Relaxed Fit Pants / 休闲裤",
          "Description": "These pants have a little more room for the legs. / 这条裤子给腿留出了更多空间。"
        },
        "10": {
          "DisplayName": "Baggy Pants / 宽松裤",
          "Description": "A loose pair of pants. / 很宽松的裤子。"
        },
        "14": {
          "DisplayName": "Polka Dot Shorts / 圆点短裤",
          "Description": "Whoops! / 哦呀！"
        },
        "7": {
          "DisplayName": "Luau Skirt / 夏威夷草裙",
          "Description": "A skirt destined to make you the 'luau' the party! / 注定让你成为派对之星的裙子！"
        },
        "2": {
          "DisplayName": "Long Dress / 长裙",
          "Description": "A long, flowy dress. / 长长的、飘逸的裙子。"
        },
        "8": {
          "DisplayName": "Genie Pants / 精灵裤",
          "Description": "Pants that balloon out near the bottom. Your wish has been answered! / 下端鼓出来的裤子。你的愿望实现了！"
        },
        "6": {
          "DisplayName": "Grass Skirt / 草裙",
          "Description": "A skirt made of dried grass. / 干草编织的裙子。"
        },
        "0": {
          "DisplayName": "Farmer Pants / 农夫裤",
          "Description": "Comfortable and durable for long hours in the field. / 舒适耐用，适合长时间田间劳作。"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Quests",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Fields": {
        "116": {
          "1": "Granny's Gift | 奶奶的礼物",
          "2": "Evelyn wants to surprise her husband with a gift. | 艾芙琳想给她丈夫一个惊喜的礼物。"
        },
        "106": {
          "1": "Cow's Delight | 讨牛欢心",
          "2": "Marnie wants to give her cows a special treat. She's asking for a single bunch of amaranth. | 玛妮想给她的奶牛一份特殊奖励。她需要一捆苋菜。"
        },
        "19": {
          "1": "The Skull Key | 头骨钥匙",
          "2": "You found a strange looking key in the bottom of the mines. | 你在矿场地底发现了一把奇怪的钥匙。"
        },
        "3": {
          "1": "The Mysterious Qi | 神秘的齐",
          "2": "You've found another note written by 'Mr. Qi'. The request is even more unusual this time. | 你又发现一张齐先生的纸条。这次的要求更加非比寻常。"
        },
        "134": {
          "1": "The Giant Stump | 大树桩",
          "2": "The big tree to the south of my farm blew down. With 100 hardwood, I could turn the stump into something interesting... | 农场南边的大树被刮倒了。如果有 100 块硬木，我可以把树桩修成有趣的东西……"
        },
        "128": {
          "1": "... | ……",
          "2": "... | ……"
        },
        "112": {
          "1": "A Favor For Clint | 克林特的小忙",
          "2": "Clint got a new hammer and he wants to test it out on a variety of metals. | 克林特弄了把新锤子，他想用不同的金属试试手感。"
        },
        "31": {
          "1": "A Winter Mystery | 冬日谜团",
          "2": "You encountered a suspicious looking figure by the bus stop. When it saw you, it fled toward town. Could there be a clue to its whereabouts? | 你在巴士站遇到了一个形迹可疑的身影。它看到你后，便向城镇逃去。那里会有线索指明它的下落吗？"
        },
        "7": {
          "1": "Raising Animals | 养殖动物",
          "2": "Robin, the local carpenter, lives north of town. In exchange for raw materials and money, she'll construct new buildings on your farm. You'll need her to build a coop or barn so that you can raise animals. | 本地的木匠罗宾就住在镇子北方。只要给她充足的原材料和金钱，她就会替你在你的农场里建造新的建筑。你需要让她帮你建造鸡舍和畜棚来饲养动物。"
        },
        "108": {
          "1": "Carving Pumpkins | 雕刻南瓜",
          "2": "Caroline wants to carve a pumpkin with her daughter. She asked you to bring her one from the farm. | 卡洛琳想为她的女儿刻一个南瓜头。她请你从农场带给她一个。"
        },
        "16": {
          "1": "Initiation | 入门",
          "2": "You successfully dispatched 10 slimes. Now you can enter the Adventurer's Guild. | 你成功消灭了 10 只史莱姆。你现在可以进入探险家公会了。"
        },
        "28": {
          "1": "Dark Talisman | 暗黑护身符",
          "2": "The Wizard asked me to retrieve the magic ink from his ex-wife's house... but to gain access I'll need a dark talisman. | 法师要我从他前妻家取回魔法墨水，…但是我需要一个暗黑护身符才能获得去往他前妻家的路。"
        },
        "121": {
          "1": "Wanted: Lobster | 征集：龙虾",
          "2": "Gus put out a notice requesting a fresh lobster. | 格斯发通知说他想要一只新鲜龙虾。"
        },
        "9": {
          "1": "Introductions | 介绍",
          "2": "It would be a nice gesture to introduce yourself around town. Some people might be anxious to meet the new farmer. | 跟镇子上的人自我介绍是很重要的。有些人会很好奇想认识新来的农夫。"
        },
        "29": {
          "1": "Strange Note | 奇怪纸条",
          "2": "You found a note, barely legible, asking you to bring \"may-pal serrup\" to the \"seecrit wuds\". | 你发现了一张模糊不清的纸条，让你把“沨唐酱”带到秘密森林。"
        },
        "23": {
          "1": "Archaeology | 考古发现",
          "2": "You found an ancient-looking object. Could it be some kind of artifact from long ago? Perhaps Gunther, curator of the local museum, has the answer. | 你发现了一个看起来很古老的东西。这会不会是远古的遗物呢？也许当地博物馆馆长冈瑟知道答案。"
        },
        "133": {
          "1": "Feeding Animals | 喂养动物",
          "2": "Robin, the local carpenter, lives north of town. In exchange for raw materials and money, she'll construct new buildings on your farm. If you build a silo, you can start harvesting your own grass with the scythe, and store it to feed your animals. | 罗宾是这里的木匠，她住在小镇的北边。你可以给她钱和原材料，让她建造新的农场建筑。等你建好筒仓，就可以用镰刀收割农场上的草，然后存起来喂养动物。"
        },
        "26": {
          "1": "\"Rat Problem\" | “老鼠肆虐”",
          "2": "There's something odd going on in the Community Center... | 社区活动中心里面好像在发生一些奇怪的事情……"
        },
        "15": {
          "1": "Initiation | 入门",
          "2": "If you can slay 10 slimes, you'll have earned your place in the Adventurer's Guild. | 只要击杀 10 只史莱姆，你就有资格进入探险家公会。"
        },
        "127": {
          "1": "Haley's Cake-Walk | 海莉的蛋糕竞走赛",
          "2": "Your wife is organizing a charity cake-walk in the town square. She asked you to bring a chocolate cake. | 你的妻子正在镇上的广场组织慈善蛋糕竞走赛。她让你带一个巧克力蛋糕。"
        },
        "105": {
          "1": "Knee Therapy | 膝盖疗养",
          "2": "George needs a hot pepper to soothe his aching knee. | 乔治需要一个辣椒来给膝盖镇痛。"
        },
        "4": {
          "1": "The Mysterious Qi | 神秘的齐",
          "2": "You've found yet another strange note within the Mayor's fridge. This time, the instructions are more cryptic. | 你发现又一张齐先生的纸条。这次的指示更加隐晦。"
        },
        "27": {
          "1": "Goblin Problem | 哥布林问题",
          "2": "There's a goblin blocking the path to the Witch's hut. There must be some way to get him to move... Perhaps I should seek out more information on Goblins. | 有一个哥布林阻塞了去往女巫小屋的路。必须要想办法让他移开……或许我应该找出更多有关哥布林的信息。"
        },
        "25": {
          "1": "How To Win Friends | 交友指南",
          "2": "Giving gifts is a great way to build friendships. Learn each person's individual tastes and you'll be popular in no time. | 送礼物是增进友谊的好办法。了解每个人的个人喜好，你快就会人见人爱了。"
        },
        "100": {
          "1": "Robin's Lost Axe | 罗宾丢失的斧子",
          "2": "Robin lost her favorite axe. The last time she remembers using it, she was cutting wood south of Marnie's ranch. | 罗宾弄丢了她最珍爱的斧子。她记得上次用它时，是在玛妮牧场的南边伐木。"
        },
        "126": {
          "1": "Errand for your Wife | 妻子的差事",
          "2": "Your wife asked you to bring her 200 pieces of fiber for a secret project. | 你的妻子让你为她的秘密工程带 200 份纤维。"
        },
        "118": {
          "1": "Aquatic Research | 水产调查",
          "2": "Demetrius is studying the toxin levels of the local pufferfish. He'd like you to bring him one. | 德米特里厄斯正在调查本地河豚的毒性。他希望你给他拿一条。"
        },
        "111": {
          "1": "A Dark Reagent | 黑暗试剂",
          "2": "The wizard wants you to descend into the mines and fetch him a Void Essence. He needs it for some kind of dark magic. | 法师想让你下矿井找一个虚空精华给他。他要用来准备一种黑暗魔法。"
        },
        "119": {
          "1": "A Soldier's Star | 士兵的星星",
          "2": "Kent wants to give his wife a starfruit for their anniversary. | 肯特想送一个杨桃给妻子当结婚纪念礼物。"
        },
        "102": {
          "1": "Mayor's \"Shorts\" | 镇长的“短裤”",
          "2": "Mayor Lewis has lost his purple \"shorts\". He's asking you to find and return them... Discreetly. | 镇长刘易斯找不到他的紫色“短裤”了。他托你悄悄地去找到后还给他……"
        },
        "8": {
          "1": "Advancement | 进阶",
          "2": "As you gain experience, you'll discover new crafting recipes to increase profit and make life easier. A scarecrow, for example, will prevent crows from snacking on your precious crops. | 随着你的经验增长，你会发现新的配方可用于增加收入和改善生活。比如说稻草人可以防止乌鸦来偷吃你的珍贵农作物。"
        },
        "6": {
          "1": "Getting Started | 开始",
          "2": "If you want to become a farmer, you have to start with the basics. Use your hoe to till the soil, then use a seed packet on the tilled soil to sow a crop. Water every day until the crop is ready for harvest. | 想要成为农夫，就要从基本开始学习。使用你的锄头锄松泥土，然后在泥土上使用种子袋以播种。每天浇水直到农作物成熟为止。"
        },
        "1": {
          "1": "Meet The Wizard | 会见法师",
          "2": "You received a letter from the local wizard. He claims to have information regarding the old community center. | 你收到本地一位法师的信件。他自称拥有关于旧社区活动中心的情报。"
        },
        "131": {
          "1": "Willy's Challenge | 威利的挑战",
          "2": "Willy has challenged you to catch 3 Sandfish. | 威利提出挑战，要你钓 3 条沙鱼。"
        },
        "132": {
          "1": "Getting Started | 新手入门",
          "2": "If you want to become a farmer, you have to start with the basics. Feed your chickens each day by letting them eat grass outside, or by placing hay into their troughs. Once they are mature, harvest an egg! | 要想成为农场主，先要做好最基础的工作。每天都要记得喂鸡，可以放它们出来吃草，也可以把干草放到饲料槽里。等鸡成熟了，就可以收获蛋了！"
        },
        "101": {
          "1": "Jodi's Request | 乔迪的请求",
          "2": "Jodi needs a fresh cauliflower for a recipe she's making. She's asking you to bring her one. | 乔迪需要用一株新鲜的花椰菜做菜。她让你带给她一株。"
        },
        "21": {
          "1": "Marnie's Request | 玛妮的请求",
          "2": "Marnie came by the farm and asked if you'd bring her a cave carrot. She's trying to train her goats to speak, and cave carrot is their favorite snack. | 玛妮来到农场，要求你为她寻找一个山洞萝卜。她正在训练她的山羊说话，而山洞萝卜是它们的最爱。"
        },
        "109": {
          "1": "Catch A Squid | 捕条鱿鱼",
          "2": "Willy is challenging you to catch a squid. He says you can fish them from the ocean on winter nights. | 威利向你发起了捕鱿鱼的挑战。他告诉你可以在冬夜的海里找到它们。"
        },
        "11": {
          "1": "Forging Ahead | 开始铸造",
          "2": "If you're going to keep mining, you should build a furnace. | 如果你想要继续采矿，就需要建造一个熔炉。"
        },
        "123": {
          "1": "Staff Of Power | 力量法杖",
          "2": "The Wizard is creating a staff of phenomenal power. Who knows what it's for. He needs an iridium bar to finish it. | 法师正在制作一把拥有惊人力量的法杖。没人知道这是干什么用的。他还差一个铱锭才能制作完成。"
        },
        "104": {
          "1": "Crop Research | 作物研究",
          "2": "Demetrius needs a fresh melon for his research. | 德米特里厄斯需要一个新鲜的甜瓜做实验。"
        },
        "12": {
          "1": "Smelting | 打铁",
          "2": "Now that you've built a furnace, you can smelt some metal. According to Clint's instructions, if you place 5 copper ore and 1 piece of coal in the furnace, it should produce a copper bar. | 你的熔炉既然打造好了，那么就可以开始打铁了。根据克林特的指示，置放 5 块铜矿石和 1 块煤炭进熔炉，应该就能生产出铜锭。"
        },
        "10": {
          "1": "Copper Ore | 铜矿石",
          "2": "You found a piece of copper ore. You're not sure what you can use it for, but the local blacksmith ought to know. | 你发现了一块铜矿石。你不确定它有何用处，但是本地的铁匠应该有所见闻。"
        },
        "14": {
          "1": "Explore The Mine | 探索矿场",
          "2": "There's an old mine shaft in the mountains north of town. There could be valuable minerals inside, but Marlon hinted that it might be dangerous. | 镇子北方山脉处有一座旧矿场。里面也许有珍贵的矿物，但是马龙说那里可能有危险。"
        },
        "110": {
          "1": "Clint's Attempt | 克林特的努力",
          "2": "Clint wants you to give Emily an amethyst. He wants you to tell her it's from him. | 克林特想让你送一个紫水晶给艾米丽。并告知她是他送的。"
        },
        "130": {
          "1": "The Pirate's Wife | 海盗的妻子",
          "2": "An old lady living on Ginger Island is asking you to find a keepsake of her husband's. She gave you an old photograph of a soldier that washed up on shore, hoping it would help in some way. | 住在姜岛上的一位老太太要你找到她丈夫的纪念品。她给了你一张冲到岸上的一位士兵的旧照片，希望它能够帮到你。"
        },
        "20": {
          "1": "Qi's Challenge | 齐先生的挑战",
          "2": "You've been challenged to reach level 25 in the skull cavern. You've been promised a substantial reward if you're successful. | 挑战要求你到达头骨山洞的第 25 层。成功的话能够获取丰厚的奖励。"
        },
        "107": {
          "1": "Blackberry Basket | 黑莓篮子",
          "2": "It's blackberry season, but Linus can't find his basket! He's asking you to help him find it. He has no idea where it is. | 又到了黑莓生长的季节，但莱纳斯找不到他的篮子了！他请你帮他找找。他也不知道丢在了哪里。"
        },
        "18": {
          "1": "To The Bottom? | 深入地底？",
          "2": "So far, there's no sign of the bottom. How low does it go? | 当前依然未发现地底最深处。这到底有多深啊？"
        },
        "22": {
          "1": "Fish Casserole | 砂锅魚",
          "2": "Jodi swung by the farm to ask you to dinner at 7:00 PM. Her only request was that you bring a largemouth bass for her fish casserole. | 乔迪来到农场邀请你在晚上 7 点去陪她吃晚餐。她的唯一的要求是你得带一条大嘴鲈鱼去给她制作砂锅鱼。"
        },
        "124": {
          "1": "Catch a Lingcod | 捕捞蛇齿单线鱼",
          "2": "Willy is challenging you to catch a Lingcod. | 威利挑战你抓一条蛇齿单线鱼。"
        },
        "13": {
          "1": "To The Beach | 前往沙滩",
          "2": "Someone named Willy invited you to visit the beach south of town. He says he has something to give you. | 一位叫威利的人邀请你前往镇子南方的沙滩。他说有东西要给你。"
        },
        "129": {
          "1": "... | ……",
          "2": "... | ……"
        },
        "125": {
          "1": "Exotic Spirits | 异域饮品",
          "2": "Gus wants to make a Coco-no-no, but he's missing the main ingredient. | 格斯想作椰子奶酒，但还差一个主要素材。"
        },
        "113": {
          "1": "Robin's Request | 罗宾的请求",
          "2": "Robin wrote to you asking for some hardwood. | 罗宾来信向你要些硬木。"
        },
        "117": {
          "1": "Pierre's Notice | 皮埃尔的布告",
          "2": "Pierre will pay \"top coin\" to whoever brings him a plate of sashimi. Apparently he's really craving the stuff. | 皮埃尔会给带给他一盘生鱼片的人“上等报酬”。很明显，他十分想吃生鱼片啊。"
        },
        "120": {
          "1": "Mayor's Need | 镇长的需求",
          "2": "Mayor Lewis wants truffle oil. He won't explain what it's for. Maybe it's none of your business. | 镇长刘易斯想要一瓶松露油。他没说是用来做什么的。也许你不该多管闲事。"
        },
        "5": {
          "1": "The Mysterious Qi | 神秘的齐",
          "2": "You found another note in the sand dragon's eye. It seems Mr. Qi's strange scavenger hunt has come to an end. | 你发现又一张齐先生的纸条。这位齐先生的奇怪要求终于到达尾声了。"
        },
        "114": {
          "1": "Fish Stew | 烩鱼汤",
          "2": "Gus wants to make fish stew, but he needs an albacore. | 格斯要做烩鱼汤，但他需要一条青花鱼。"
        },
        "24": {
          "1": "Archaeology | 考古发现",
          "2": "Gunther asked if you'd consider donating any new artifacts or minerals you find to the museum. He says he'll compensate you by way of occasional rare goods. | 冈瑟询问你是否能考虑把新发现的古物或矿石捐献给博物馆。他说他会回报以一些稀有的货物。"
        },
        "17": {
          "1": "Deeper In The Mine | 矿场深处",
          "2": "It seems that the mine elevator is still functional. It will allow you to quickly return to any elevator doors you've discovered. A deeper expedition might be in order. | 看来矿场的升降机依然能用。你能够通过它快速回到你之前发现过的任何升降机门口。现在可以更加深入矿场了。"
        },
        "115": {
          "1": "Fresh Fruit | 新鲜水果",
          "2": "Emily wants a taste of spring. She's asking for a fresh apricot. | 艾米丽想尝尝春天的味道。她想要一个新鲜的杏子。"
        },
        "103": {
          "1": "Pam Is Thirsty | 潘姆渴了",
          "2": "Pam is hankerin' for a pale ale. Regular old beer won't do. You can brew one yourself if you have hops and a keg. | 潘姆想喝淡啤酒。普通的老啤酒不会有用的。如果你有啤酒花和酿造桶，就可以自己酿一杯了。"
        },
        "122": {
          "1": "Pam Needs Juice | 潘姆需要电池",
          "2": "Pam's TV Remote is dead. She's having a tough time going back and forth between the couch and the TV dial. | 潘姆的电视遥控器没电了。她在沙发和电视控制面板之间来来回回地走太累了。"
        },
        "30": {
          "1": "Cryptic Note | 秘文纸条",
          "2": "You found a note that reads, \"Someone is waiting for you on level 100 in the Skull Cavern\" | 你找到一张纸条，上面写道：“有人在骷髅洞的第 100 层等你”"
        },
        "2": {
          "1": "The Mysterious Qi | 神秘的齐",
          "2": "Within a secret lock-box, you found a note with peculiar instructions. It's signed by a 'Mr. Qi'. | 在一个隐秘的加密箱里，你发现了一张写着指示的纸条。署名者是齐先生的纸条。"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/SecretNotes",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "1": "It's a page from Abigail's Diary / 这是阿比盖尔日记中的一页^^'Things I love: the smell of carved pumpkin, keeping an amethyst under my pillow, chocolate cake, the thrill of spicy eel, and the comfort of Mom's blackberry cobbler (I like to eat!)'%revealtaste:Abigail:276%revealtaste:Abigail:66%revealtaste:Abigail:220%revealtaste:Abigail:226%revealtaste:Abigail:611 / “我喜欢的事物：雕刻南瓜的香气、在我的枕头下放块紫水晶、巧克力蛋糕、香辣鳗鱼的刺激，以及妈妈做的黑莓脆皮饼带来的慰藉（我爱吃！）”%revealtaste:Abigail:276%revealtaste:Abigail:66%revealtaste:Abigail:220%revealtaste:Abigail:226%revealtaste:Abigail:611",
        "21": "!image 5 / !image 5",
        "11": "!image 6 / !image 6",
        "19": "!image 2 / !image 2",
        "3": "It's written in Leah's handwriting / 这是莉亚的笔迹写的。^^My idea of a perfect dinner would be salad, goat cheese, truffle, and wine. For dessert I'd need a poppyseed muffin. Yum! If someone gave me one of those things, I'd melt.%revealtaste:Leah:196%revealtaste:Leah:426%revealtaste:Leah:430%revealtaste:Leah:348%revealtaste:Leah:651 / 我对完美晚餐的构想是沙拉、山羊乳酪、松露和果酒。至于甜点，我需要一个虞美人籽松糕。好吃！如果有人给我其中之一，我会很感动的。%revealtaste:Leah:196%revealtaste:Leah:426%revealtaste:Leah:430%revealtaste:Leah:348%revealtaste:Leah:651",
        "12": "I've found some good things by looking in the garbage cans, on lucky days. / 在走运的日子里，我在垃圾桶里找到了一些好东西。^^Sometimes you'll find the 'dish of the day' behind the saloon... usually fresh! / 有时你会在星之果实餐吧的垃圾桶里找到“当日特供”……通常还很新鲜！^^For dessert, I'll check the Mullners' can for cookies. / 至于甜点，我会翻翻乔治·莫尔纳家的垃圾桶，看看有没有饼干。^^For treasures, check the cans by the blacksmith and museum. / 珍宝的话，我会看看铁匠铺和博物馆旁的垃圾桶。",
        "10": "Someone is  / 有人^    waiting for you  /     在^        on level 100  /       头骨山洞^         in /       的^          the /       第 100 层^             skull cavern... /       等你……",
        "14": "^^^    I hid something behind the community center. /     我在社区中心背面藏了些东西。",
        "1009": "'Twas a rain drenched day, and upon a lonely rock a beautiful maiden saw I / 那是一个阴雨天，我看见美丽的少女孤独地坐在岩石之上。^^Tales I'd heard of sea-born maidens singing siren's songs, / 传说有海的女儿们歌唱海妖之歌，^Yet nary a note could she muster... / 但是她却拼不出半个音符……^^The next morning I spied an arrangement of stone upon the foamy bank... / 第二天早上，我发现满是泡沫的岸上有一排石头……^----------------- / ——————————^Aye... stones as big as 'ones' and stones as big as 'fives' were they... / 对……有一分钱硬币那么大的石头，也有五分钱那么大的……^----------------- / ——————————^If but this harried sea dog a tune could howl, perhaps to Blackgull's treasure would she lead... / 要是我这副老嗓子能吼出什么曲调，也许她能带领我去寻找黑海鸥的宝藏……",
        "7": "It's a page from someone's diary... / 这是某人日记中的一页……^^...There are only a few 'older' bachelors in town, and none of them are perfect! Harvey is really anxious and weak, but I know he would make a loyal and devoted husband. He likes coffee and pickles. / ……镇里只有少数几个“老”单身汉，他们都并不完美！哈维确实焦虑而软弱，但我知道他会成为一个忠诚专一的丈夫。他喜欢咖啡和腌菜。^^Elliott is a bit foppish and melodramatic, but he does have a nice chin. He likes crab cakes and pomegranates. / 艾利欧特有些浮夸和矫情，但他的下巴确实很好看。他喜欢蟹黄糕和石榴。^^Shane is messy and anti-social. But I think his gruff exterior is a defense mechanism, insulating his softness from the world. He likes Beer, Pizza, and Pepper Poppers.%revealtaste:Harvey:395%revealtaste:Harvey:342%revealtaste:Elliott:732%revealtaste:Elliott:637%revealtaste:Shane:346%revealtaste:Shane:206%revealtaste:Shane:215 / 谢恩邋遢且反社会。但我认为他粗鲁的外在是一种保护机制，将他内心的柔软与世界隔离开来。他喜欢啤酒、披萨和爆炒青椒。%revealtaste:Harvey:395%revealtaste:Harvey:342%revealtaste:Elliott:732%revealtaste:Elliott:637%revealtaste:Shane:346%revealtaste:Shane:206%revealtaste:Shane:215",
        "20": "!image 4 / !image 4",
        "18": "!image 3 / !image 3",
        "16": "!image 0 / !image 0",
        "1002": "Day 6 / 第 6 天^^I won't go hungry here... the waters are full of edible (nay, delicious!) fish. / 我在这里再也不会挨饿了……水里全是可以吃的（不对，是很美味的！）鱼。^^I even caught a stingray in the caves by the southeast shore. I haven't a clue what to do with it, though! / 我甚至在东南海岸的洞穴里抓到了一条黄貂鱼。不过我不知道该怎么处理！^^The other day, I even fished up a couple of golden walnuts. They seem to be all over the island. The local parrots go crazy for them! / 前些日子，我甚至捞到了几个金色核桃。它们似乎遍布全岛。当地的鹦鹉抢疯了！",
        "22": "Greetings, @... / 欢迎， @……^^Have you found my 'secret' in the dark tunnel? / 你已在黑暗隧道中找到了我的“秘密”吗？^^I look forward to meeting you! / 我期待着与你会面！^^    -Qi / ——齐",
        "1010": "!image 9 / !image 9",
        "9": "Alex's Strength Training Diet: / 亚历克斯的力量训练食谱：^^*Complete Breakfast / *完美早餐^*Salmon Dinner / *鲑鱼晚餐^^(I've learned to love this food... I can feel the protein!!)%revealtaste:Alex:201%revealtaste:Alex:212 / （我已学会爱上这些食物……我感受到了蛋白质的力量！！）%revealtaste:Alex:201%revealtaste:Alex:212",
        "23": "^^^If yoo can reed dis... come to seecrit wuds. Pleez bring may-pal serrup. / 如果伲渎到着个……到密谜竖林来。清带点沨唐酱。",
        "1003": "Day 14 / 第 14 天^^After half a month on this island, I've learned a thing or two about finding these golden nuts. / 在这个岛上待了半个月后，我对如何找到这些金色坚果已经略懂门道了。^^One must keep their eyes peeled for subtle clues. If something looks unusual, there may be a hidden nut nearby. / 必须要睁大眼睛寻找微小的线索，如果有什么东西看起来不同寻常，那附近可能就有个隐藏的坚果。^^I've noticed signs in the sand... and signs in the leaves... / 我发现沙子里有……树叶里也有……^^I even saw a nut up in a tree near the volcano. If only I had a way of shooting it down... / 我甚至在火山附近的一棵树上看到了一个坚果。可惜我没办法把它打下来……^^Whenever I've spotted a nut plant, I've always found a way to reach it. / 每次我发现有坚果的植株时，总能找到方法去够到它。",
        "26": "Ancient Farming Secrets, line 37: / 《古代农耕秘辛》第 37 行：^^There's no better helper than a raisin-fed Junimo... / 喂祝尼魔吃葡萄干，它们干起活来可带劲了……^^",
        "1005": "Day 23 / 第 23 天^^The local volcano holds many secrets. / 当地的火山埋藏着许多秘密。^^I've seen little men with glowing eyes, skittering about in the dark... like cats in the night. / 我看到眼睛发光的小人，在黑暗里四处蹦跳，就像夜里的猫……^^(Could these be the fabled dwarf-men, mentioned by M. Jasper in his 'Famous Journeys'?) / （他们是不是 M·贾思博在他的《闻名之旅》里提到的矮人？）^^Strange machines, too. Uncanny... not like anything known to man. / 我还看到有奇怪的机器，怪异离奇，不像是人类已知的东西。^^At the top, I found a passage to the caldera of the volcano. And, half submerged in the bubbling lava, a peculiar machine... a kind of \"forge\".  / 在山顶，我找到了一条通往火山口的通道。还有，半淹没在冒泡的熔岩中，有一台奇特的机器……是一种“锻造炉”。 ^^I'll investigate further tomorrow. / 我明天会继续调查。",
        "13": "^^12 o'clock noon SHARP. Last day of the season. Check the bush above the playground. / 每个季节最后一天的中午 12 点整，检查一下游乐场上方的灌木丛吧。",
        "15": "^^       Mermaid Show: 1-5-4-2-3 /        美人鱼秀：1-5-4-2-3",
        "4": "It's a note of Maru's / 这是玛鲁的笔记^^Parts still needed for my greatest invention yet! / 我最伟大的发明还需要一些部件！^^*Gold Bar / *金锭^*Iridium Bar / *铱锭^*Battery Pack / *电池组^*Diamond / *钻石^*Strawberries%revealtaste:Maru:336%revealtaste:Maru:337%revealtaste:Maru:787%revealtaste:Maru:72%revealtaste:Maru:400 / *草莓%revealtaste:Maru:336%revealtaste:Maru:337%revealtaste:Maru:787%revealtaste:Maru:72%revealtaste:Maru:400",
        "27": "My dear grandchild, / 亲爱的孩子：^By the time you find this note, I expect you'll have been living in the valley for quite some time. I hope things are going well! / 你找到这张纸条的时候，想必已经在星露谷住了很长一段时间了吧。希望你的生活一切顺利！^I'm honored that you're continuing the family tradition of farming, and through that noble endeavor, bringing greater life and abundance to all of Stardew Valley... a place very dear to my heart. / 星露谷对我来说是一个很亲切的地方……你能继承家里耕种的传统，用朴素的行动给这里带来生机和富饶，我感到非常光荣。^Keep up the good work! / 继续加油吧！^^-Grandpa / ——爷爷^^P.S. ...I've hidden a very special secret for you somewhere in the valley. You might think of it as a compendium of my greatest discoveries. Someday, when you're ready, you'll find it. / 附：……我在山谷的某个地方给你留了一个特别的秘密，那里汇集了我找到的最厉害的东西。等你准备好的时候，自然会找到的。",
        "1006": "!image 8 / !image 8",
        "25": "^^ I 'borrowed' a necklace from Mom, but lost it somewhere near the bath house... She's going to freak out if she notices it's missing! / 我向妈妈借了一条项链，但在澡堂附近丢了……如果她发现项链不见了，肯定会大发雷霆！",
        "1011": "Day 37 / 第 37 天^^When I was a boy of ten years old, my father gave me a glow ring and a magnet ring. They've never left my fingers since. / 我十岁的时候，父亲给了我一个光辉戒指和一个磁铁戒指。从那以后我就一直戴着它们。^^However, when I was standing on top of the volcano... a strange idea came over me. / 但是，当我站在火山顶上的时候……我突然有了一个奇怪的想法。^^I took my two rings, and cast them into the forge. / 我拿出我的两个戒指，把它们扔进了锻造炉。^^Lo and behold! They combined into one! / 天哪！它们合二为一了！^^Now I've got one glowing magnet ring... I hope old pappy doesn't mind, rest his soul... / 现在我拥有了一个光辉磁铁戒指……我希望老父亲不会介意，愿他的灵魂安息……",
        "1007": "--Forging Table-- / ——锻造表——^^Topaz -- Defense / 黄水晶 —— 防御^Emerald -- Speed / 绿宝石 —— 速度^Jade -- Critical Strike Power / 翡翠 —— 暴击能量^Aquamarine -- Critical Strike Chance / 海蓝宝石 —— 暴击几率^Amethyst -- Knockback / 紫水晶 —— 击退^Ruby -- Damage / 红宝石 —— 伤害^^Prismatic Shard -- Enchantment / 五彩碎片 —— 附魔^^Note: Weapons can be forged up to 3 times with gems, and can also be enchanted once with a prismatic shard. / 备注：武器可以用宝石锻造三次，也可以用五彩碎片附魔一次。^^Note 2: 'Innate Enchantments', (meaning those powers that sometimes appear on weapons when you first acquire them), can also be added or re-discovered using a Dragon Tooth. It's theorized that this cannot be done to weapons above a certain caliber. / 备注 2：“固有附魔”（获得武器时自带的属性）可以使用龙牙来增加或刷新。据推测，一定品质之上的武器无法获得此类附魔。^^Tools can only be enchanted, not forged. / 工具只能附魔，不能锻造。",
        "5": "It's Penny's handwriting: / 看起来像是潘妮的笔迹：^^I want to get everyone something they love! / 我想给每个人买他们喜欢的东西！^^Mom: Parsnip, Glazed Yams, NO BEER! / 妈妈：防风草、琉璃山药、不要啤酒！^Jas: Fairy Rose, Plum Pudding / 贾斯：玫瑰仙子、葡萄干布丁^Vincent: Pink Cake, Grape / 文森特：粉红蛋糕、葡萄^Mr. Mullner: Leek, Fried Mushroom / 莫尔纳先生：韭葱、炒蘑菇^Granny Mullner: Beet, Tulip%revealtaste:Pam:24%revealtaste:Pam:208%revealtaste:Pam:346%revealtaste:Jas:595%revealtaste:Jas:604%revealtaste:Vincent:398%revealtaste:Vincent:221%revealtaste:George:20%revealtaste:George:205%revealtaste:Evelyn:284%revealtaste:Evelyn:591 / 莫尔纳奶奶：甜菜、郁金香%revealtaste:Pam:24%revealtaste:Pam:208%revealtaste:Pam:346%revealtaste:Jas:595%revealtaste:Jas:604%revealtaste:Vincent:398%revealtaste:Vincent:221%revealtaste:George:20%revealtaste:George:205%revealtaste:Evelyn:284%revealtaste:Evelyn:591",
        "1004": "!image 10 / !image 10",
        "24": "It's a page from M. Jasper's book: / 这是 M·贾思博的书中的一页：^^...the creatures, known by some as \"Forest Spirits\" or \"Junimos\", are said to appear in abandoned buildings after they've \"gone to seed\". / ……这些生物，有一些人称之为“森林精灵”或是“祝尼魔”。据说它们会出现在废弃破败的建筑物之中。^^As a general rule... when humans leave, and nature begins to reclaim her territory, the Junimos will undoubtedly appear. / 通常来说……当人类离开一个地方，大自然开始收回她的领土时，祝尼魔就一定会出现。^^Folk wisdom holds that the Junimos display some kind of resonant affinity with gemstones that are placed inside their little huts... / 民间传说认为，祝尼魔跟他们的小屋里放置的宝石会显示出某种共鸣关系……^^Also, it's said that raisins are their favorite food, but they are too shy to take them directly from the hand. / 另外，据说他们最喜欢吃葡萄干，不过很腼腆，不敢直接从人的手上拿。^^Of course, all these claims come from dubious, unverified sources... As far as I know, even the mere existence of these creatures has never been proven! / 当然，这些说法的来源都很可疑，未经验证……据我所知，甚至还没有任何实际证据表明这种生物确实存在！",
        "17": "!image 1 / !image 1",
        "1001": "Day 1 / 第 1 天^^...My ship is lost... Shattered by a tempest in the unforgiving sea. / ……我的船没了……它在暴风雨中被无情的大海摧毁了。^^I find myself stranded now, on these strange shores. My crew has perished, but I still live. Perhaps lady luck has blessed these wicked bones of mine... Or has her own designs for my fate... / 我现在被困在这片陌生的海岸上。我的船员都去世了，只有我还活着。也许幸运女神保佑了我这把恶事做尽的老骨头……也有可能她对我的命运还有其他的安排。^^At any rate, I've no choice but to make a life for myself here. There's fresh water in abundance, food to forage, and fertile soil to work. / 不管怎样，我别无选择，只能在这个地方过日子了。有充足的淡水，有食物可以采集，有肥沃的土壤可以耕种……^^First I'll build a shelter... / 首先我得建一个住处……^^(There are some pages missing) / （有几页缺失了）",
        "2": "It's Sam's holiday shopping list / 这是山姆的假日购物清单^^Everyone's favorites / 每个人的最爱^^Sebastian: Frozen Tear, Sashimi / 塞巴斯蒂安：泪晶、生鱼片^Penny: Emerald, Poppy / 潘妮：绿宝石、虞美人花^Vincent: Grape, Cranberry Candy / 文森特：葡萄、蔓越莓糖果^Mom: Crispy Bass, Pancakes / 妈妈：香酥鲈鱼、薄煎饼^Dad: Risotto, Roasted Hazelnuts / 爸爸：意式蕨菜炖饭、烤榛子^Me: Cactus, Maple Bar, Pizza%revealtaste:Sebastian:84%revealtaste:Sebastian:227%revealtaste:Penny:60%revealtaste:Penny:376%revealtaste:Vincent:398%revealtaste:Vincent:612%revealtaste:Jodi:214%revealtaste:Jodi:211%revealtaste:Kent:649%revealtaste:Kent:607%revealtaste:Sam:90%revealtaste:Sam:731%revealtaste:Sam:206 / 我：仙人掌果子、枫糖棒、披萨%revealtaste:Sebastian:84%revealtaste:Sebastian:227%revealtaste:Penny:60%revealtaste:Penny:376%revealtaste:Vincent:398%revealtaste:Vincent:612%revealtaste:Jodi:214%revealtaste:Jodi:211%revealtaste:Kent:649%revealtaste:Kent:607%revealtaste:Sam:90%revealtaste:Sam:731%revealtaste:Sam:206",
        "8": "^To Haley and Emily / 致海莉和艾米丽^^Hope you two are doing well! We've sent you your favorite gifts: Pink Cake and Sunflowers for Haley, Gemstones and Wool for Emily! / 希望你们俩一切安好！给你们寄了最爱的礼物：海莉的粉红蛋糕和向日葵，艾米丽的宝石和动物毛！^^-Love Mom and Dad%revealtaste:Haley:221%revealtaste:Haley:421%revealtaste:Emily:440%revealtaste:Emily:66%revealtaste:Emily:62%revealtaste:Emily:60%revealtaste:Emily:70%revealtaste:Emily:64%revealtaste:Emily:68 / ——爱你们的妈妈和爸爸。%revealtaste:Haley:221%revealtaste:Haley:421%revealtaste:Emily:440%revealtaste:Emily:66%revealtaste:Emily:62%revealtaste:Emily:60%revealtaste:Emily:70%revealtaste:Emily:64%revealtaste:Emily:68",
        "6": "Stardrop Saloon Special Orders / 星之果实餐吧特别订单^^Mayor Lewis: Autumn's Bounty / 刘易斯镇长：秋日恩赐^(Double order of high-fiber bread on the side) / （配两份高纤维面包）^^Marnie: Pumpkin Pie / 玛妮：南瓜派^(extra whipped cream!) / （多加鲜奶油！）^^Demetrius: Bean Hotpot / 德米特里厄斯：豆类火锅^(Make it spicy) / （加辣）^^Caroline: Fish Taco / 卡洛琳：鱼肉卷^(she wants triple the sauce! Better throw in a few extra napkins...)%revealtaste:Lewis:235%revealtaste:Marnie:608%revealtaste:Demetrius:207%revealtaste:Caroline:213 / （她要三倍酱汁！最好多放几张餐巾纸……）%revealtaste:Lewis:235%revealtaste:Marnie:608%revealtaste:Demetrius:207%revealtaste:Caroline:213",
        "1008": "--Weapon Enchantments-- / ——武器附魔——^^Artful: Allows you to do \"special moves\" more rapidly / 巧妙：能让你更快地做出“特殊动作”。^^Bug Killer: Do more damage to bugs. / 虫子杀手：对虫子造成更多伤害。^^Vampiric: Occasionally siphon health from a monster. / 吸血：偶尔能从怪物身上吸取生命。^^Crusader: Do more damage to \"unholy\" monsters. / 十字军：对“邪恶”怪物造成更多伤害。^^Haymaker: When cutting weeds, you get more fiber, and also a chance to collect hay. / 干草：割杂草时，你会得到更多的纤维，也有几率获得干草。^^--Tool Enchantments-- / ——工具附魔——^^Powerful: Do more tool damage to stones, trees, and the like. / 强力：对石头、树木等造成更多工具伤害。^^Reaching: Increases your charge-up capacity, for a greater area of effect. / 范围：增强蓄力能力，作用范围更大。^^Shaving: Chance to peel off additional wood when chopping. / 木屑：砍树时有几率获得额外的木材。^^Bottomless: Watering can will never run dry. / 无底洞：喷壶永远不会干涸。^^Generous: Dig up more from beneath the earth. / 丰富：能从地下挖出更多东西。^^Archaeologist: Greater chance to find artifacts and bones. / 考古学家：有更高几率发现文物和骨头。^^Efficient: Takes no energy to use. / 省力：使用不费体力。^^Swift: Swing the tool faster. / 迅捷：更快地挥动工具。^^Master: Increases fishing level. / 精通：提升钓鱼等级。^^Auto-Hook: Automatically hooks fish when they bite. / 自动上钩：鱼咬钩时自动开始钓鱼。^^Preserving: Bait and tackle have a 50% chance to not be consumed. / 耐用：有 50% 的几率不消耗鱼饵和渔具。"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Achievements",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "19": "Living Large / 富裕生活^Upgrade your house to the maximum size. / 将房屋升级至最大号。^true^18^15",
        "3": "Millionaire (1mil) / 百万富翁(100万)^Earn 1,000,000g / 赚取 1,000,000 金^true^2^1",
        "31": "Polyculture / 混合栽培^Ship 15 of each crop. / 每种作物运送 15 份。^true^-1^34",
        "7": "Best Friends / 最好的朋友^Reach a 10-heart friend level with someone. / 与某人达到了 10 颗心的等级。^true^6^31",
        "36": "Two Thumbs Up / 意犹未尽^See a movie. / 看一部电影。^false^-1^9",
        "16": "Sous Chef / 副主厨师^Cook 25 different recipes. / 做出 25 道不同的料理。^true^15^7",
        "28": "Treasure Trove / 无主宝藏^Donate 40 different items to the museum. / 向博物馆捐赠 40 种不同的物品。^true^-1^6",
        "41": "Danger In The Deep / 深处的危险^Reach the bottom of the 'dangerous' mines. / 到达“危险”矿井的底层。^false^-1^9",
        "9": "The Beloved Farmer / 深受喜爱的农夫^Reach a 10-heart friend level with 8 people. / 与 8 个人达到了 10 颗心的等级。^true^7^32",
        "29": "Gofer / 听差^Complete 10 'Help Wanted' requests. / 完成 10 个“需要帮助”任务。^true^-1^22",
        "32": "Monoculture / 单一栽培^Ship 300 of one crop. / 一种作物运送 300 份。^true^-1^33",
        "26": "Master Angler / 垂钓大师^Catch every fish. / 抓住所有种类的鱼。^true^25^24",
        "15": "Cook / 厨子^Cook 10 different recipes. / 做出 10 道不同的料理。^true^18^12",
        "4": "Legend (10mil) / 千万富翁(1000万)^Earn 10,000,000g / 赚取 10,000,000 金^false^-1^3",
        "27": "Mother Catch / 捕鱼大师^Catch 100 fish. / 抓住 100 条鱼。^true^64^30",
        "25": "Ol' Mariner / 老海员^Catch 24 different fish. / 抓住 24 种不同的鱼。^true^24^5",
        "35": "Well-read / 博览群书^Read every book. / 读完所有的书。^true^-1^9",
        "42": "Infinite Power / 无限力量^Obtain the most powerful weapon. / 获得最强大的武器。^true^-1^9",
        "6": "A New Friend / 新朋友^Reach a 5-heart friend level with someone. / 与某人达到了 5 颗心的等级。^true^-1^14",
        "40": "A Distant Shore / 遥远的海岸^Reach Ginger Island. / 到达姜岛。^false^-1^9",
        "1": "Cowpoke (50k) / 牛仔（5万）^Earn 50,000g / 赚取 50,000 金^true^0^21",
        "34": "Full Shipment / 全部货物^Ship every item. / 寄出每一种物品。^true^-1^9",
        "21": "Artisan / 工匠^Craft 30 different items. / 制作 30 个不同的物品。^true^20^16",
        "11": "Cliques / 朋友圈^Reach a 5-heart friend level with 4 people. / 与 4 个人达到了 5 颗心的等级。^true^6^26",
        "12": "Networking / 广结好友^Reach a 5-heart friend level with 10 people. / 与 10 个人达到了 5 颗心的等级。^true^11^25",
        "39": "Good Neighbors / 热心邻居^Help your forest neighbors grow their family. / 帮助森林里的邻居朋友组建家庭。^true^-1^9",
        "20": "D.I.Y. / 自己动手^Craft 15 different items. / 制作 15 个不同的物品。^true^-1^29",
        "18": "Moving Up / 节节高升^Upgrade your house. / 升级你的房屋。^true^-1^13",
        "37": "Blue Ribbon / 冠军^Get 1st place in the Stardew Valley Fair competition. / 在星露谷集市的比赛中获得第一名。^true^-1^9",
        "22": "Craft Master / 制造大师^Craft every item. / 制作所有物品。^true^21^23",
        "0": "Greenhorn (15k) / 新手（1.5万）^Earn 15,000g / 赚取 15,000 金^true^-1^18",
        "13": "Popular / 万人迷^Reach a 5-heart friend level with 20 people. / 与 20 个人达到了 5 颗心的等级。^true^12^11",
        "44": "Perfection / 完美^Reach the summit. / 到达山顶。^false^-1^9",
        "5": "A Complete Collection / 全套收集^Complete the museum collection. / 完成博物馆收集。^true^28^0",
        "24": "Fisherman / 渔夫^Catch 10 different fish. / 抓住 10 种不同的鱼。^true^-1^28",
        "17": "Gourmet Chef / 美食大厨^Cook every recipe. / 烹饪每种配方^true^16^35",
        "38": "An Unforgettable Soup / 难忘的汤^Delight the Governor. / 让州长高兴。^true^-1^9",
        "30": "A Big Help / 帮了大忙^Complete 40 'Help Wanted' requests. / 完成 40 个“需要帮助”任务。^true^29^10",
        "2": "Homesteader (250k) / 农场主（25万）^Earn 250,000g / 赚取 250,000 金^true^1^20"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/EngagementDialogue",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Fields": {
        "Leah1": {
          "0": "I've always dreamed of living on a farm.$h#$e#I'm going to be so happy. | 我一直渴望着能够住进农场。$h#$e#我简直太高兴了。"
        },
        "Harvey0": {
          "0": "Oh my goodness! I have so much to prepare before the wedding! I'm nervous.$l#$e#I'll be relieved after we're all settled in on your farm.$h | 天哪！婚礼还有那么多事情要准备！紧张死了。$l#$e#只有等在你的农场里安顿下来后，我才能歇会了。$h"
        },
        "Emily0": {
          "0": "Can you believe we're about to move in together? I've never lived with anyone but my family.#$e#It's... exciting. | 你能相信我们要搬一起住了吗？我除了和家人还从没和其他人住一起过。#$e#真……刺激。"
        },
        "Harvey1": {
          "0": "I'm really happy.$h#$e#This was always my secret wish.$l | 我真的好开心啊。$h#$e#这一直以来都是我内心深处的愿望。$l"
        },
        "Emily1": {
          "0": "I always knew something important would happen between us... I just never thought it would be this!$h#$e#The parrot is excited too. | 我就知道我俩之间会有些重大的事情发生……但我从来没想到会是这个！$h#$e#连鹦鹉都很兴奋啊。"
        },
        "Elliott1": {
          "0": "This is going to be such an adventure! I'm really excited. Aren't you?$h#$e#We can use my cottage as a beach house.$l | 这将是一场大冒险！我好激动。你也是吧？$h#$e#我们可以把我的小屋当作海滨别墅。$l"
        },
        "Alex0": {
          "0": "@, this is the greatest thing that could have happened.$l#$e#I can't wait.$h | @，这是这个世上最棒的事情。$l#$e#我已经等不及了。$h"
        },
        "Abigail0": {
          "0": "Hehe. Me? Married? I never thought this would happen.$h#$e#We're going to have a lot of fun together.$h | 呵呵。我？结婚？我从没想过这会成真。$h#$e#我们在一起会很开心的。$h"
        },
        "Maru1": {
          "0": "I need to get mentally prepared for being a farmer's wife. | 我得做好成为农夫的妻子的心理准备。"
        },
        "Alex1": {
          "0": "I'm going to love being a farmer.$h | 我一定会爱上农夫的生活的。$h"
        },
        "Krobus0": {
          "0": "@... I'm afraid we'll have to keep this a secret... Neither my people nor yours would accept us living together. | @……恐怕我们必须得保密……我和你的同族人都不会接受我们住在一起。"
        },
        "Penny0": {
          "0": "@.. I'm a little scared. This is such a big change!#$e#Don't worry, I'm really happy, too.$h | @…我有些害怕。这是天翻地覆的变化！#$e#别担心，我真的很高兴。$h"
        },
        "Abigail1": {
          "0": "I'm engaged to a farmer. Wow!$h#$e#Our lives are going to be a lot different from now on.$l | 我和一个农夫订婚了。哇！$h#$e#从现在开始，我们的生活将截然不同。$l"
        },
        "Krobus1": {
          "0": "You know I'll be a very strange person to live with, right? I won't be able to leave the house... | 你应该明白跟我一起住会感觉我很奇怪的，是吧？毕竟我不能出门……"
        },
        "Sebastian1": {
          "0": "When you showed up in town, I never thought I'd be marrying you some day.$l#$e#Life is strange, huh?$h | 你刚出现在镇上那会儿，我可想不到会有和你结婚的那一天。$l#$e#生命真是奇妙，对不对？$h"
        },
        "Haley0": {
          "0": "I'm so happy!$h#$e#It's just like I always dreamed.$l | 我好高兴啊！$h#$e#我终于要美梦成真了。$l"
        },
        "Shane0": {
          "0": "Part of me is wondering if this isn't all some elaborate prank.#$e#I can't believe you'd actually want to marry someone like me. | 我不禁怀疑这一切只是个精心策划的恶作剧。#$e#我简直不敢相信你会真的想和我这样的人结婚。"
        },
        "Haley1": {
          "0": "It's okay. I know we can't have a honeymoon, since your farm needs to be taken care of.#$e#I'm a farmer now, too! | 没关系。我知道你要照顾农场，所以没法儿度蜜月。#$e#我现在也是种庄稼的人了！"
        },
        "Penny1": {
          "0": "We're going to have a little farm family, soon.$l#$e#I'm so glad you feel this way about me.$h | 我们很快就会组成一个小小的农户家庭。$l#$e#真高兴你那么喜欢我。$h"
        },
        "Sebastian0": {
          "0": "In a couple days I'm going to be living on a farm. I can't believe it.$h#$e#I'm happy, though.$l | 几天后我就要在农场开始新生活了。这简直难以置信。$h#$e#可是我也好高兴啊。$l"
        },
        "Elliott0": {
          "0": "The farm will be such a lovely place to write. I'm really looking forward to this.$h#$e#We're going to make a great pair.$l | 农场是一个值得大书特书的好地方。我好期待啊。$h#$e#我们会成为让人羡慕的夫妻。$l"
        },
        "Sam1": {
          "0": "I never dreamed this would happen. I'm so lucky.$l#$e#I can't wait till the wedding.$h | 我从没想过这会成真。我太幸运了。$l#$e#我等不及举行婚礼了。$h"
        },
        "Leah0": {
          "0": "...$l#$e#I'm a little nervous. But happy.$h | ……$l#$e#我有点紧张。但是也很高兴。$h"
        },
        "Shane1": {
          "0": "@... My head's spinning, and I haven't even had a beer today. | @……我头好晕,我今天连啤酒都没喝。"
        },
        "Sam0": {
          "0": "I'm going to be really happy as your husband, @.$l#$e#I'm excited. | 作为你的丈夫，我会非常幸福，@。$l#$e#我好激动。"
        },
        "Maru0": {
          "0": "I'm really excited.$h#$b#I'm going to be your wife. Hehe.$l | 我好激动。$h#$b#我就要嫁给你了。呵呵。$l"
        }
      }
    },
