      "Fields": {
        "Lewis": {
          "0": "Wow, this is my favorite! Thank you! | 哇哦，这是我的最爱！非常感谢！",
          "2": "Thanks, this is great! | 谢谢，这个好棒！",
          "4": "Well, I guess it's the thought that counts... | 好吧，我想心意到了就行了……",
          "6": "This makes me sick. What a horrendous gift. | 这让我觉得恶心。多可怕的礼物啊。",
          "8": "That's very nice of you. Thanks. | 你真是太好了。感谢啊。"
        },
        "Wizard": {
          "0": "Ahh, this is imbued with potent arcane energies. It's very useful for my studies. Thank you! | 啊，这里面充满了强大的奥术能量。这会给我的研究带来巨大的帮助。非常感谢！",
          "2": "Many thanks. This item has some very interesting properties. | 非常感谢。这东西有一些很有趣的属性。",
          "4": "This?... I suppose I'll cast it into the flames and see what happens. | 这个？……我想我可以把它投入火里，然后看看会发生什么。",
          "6": "Ughh... These are utterly mundane. Please refrain from bothering me with this in the future. | 呃……这些东西很普通。请你以后不要再用它们打扰我。",
          "8": "Thank you. This will prove useful, I think. | 谢谢。我想这会很有用的。"
        },
        "Willy": {
          "0": "This is great! If only me ol' Pappy was around. He'd go nuts for this. | 真是太棒了！如果我的老爹还活着，看到这个他会抓狂的。",
          "2": "This looks great. Thank you! | 这看起来很不错。非常感谢！",
          "4": "Hmmm... You like stuff like this? Huh. | 嗯……你喜欢这种东西？哈",
          "6": "... *sniff*... Well I guess I can toss it into the chum bucket. | ……*吸气*……我想我可以把它扔到鱼饵桶里。",
          "8": "A gift! Thanks. | 一个礼物！谢谢你啊。"
        },
        "Krobus": {
          "0": "This is an amazing gift. For my people it is a great honor to receive something like this. | 这真是份惊艳的礼物。收到这个东西，在我的族里可以说是很荣幸的事情。",
          "2": "Thank you very much. | 非常感谢你。",
          "4": "Humans have... interesting tastes. | 人类的口味……还真是有趣。",
          "6": "Oh... Um. I guess I'll accept it. | 噢！嗯。我会收下的。",
          "8": "Thank you. | 谢谢。"
        },
        "Universal_Dislike": {
          "0": "-4 -8 -12 -15 -16 -19 -22 -24 -25 -28 -74 78 169 246 247 305 309 310 311 403 419 423 535 536 537 725 726 749 271 Book_PriceCatalogue category_trinket | -4 -8 -12 -15 -16 -19 -22 -24 -25 -28 -74 78 169 246 247 305 309 310 311 403 419 423 535 536 537 725 726 749 271 Book_PriceCatalogue category_trinket"
        },
        "Vincent": {
          "0": "Wow, thank you so much! This is terrific! | 哇哦，太感谢你了！好极了！",
          "2": "For me? Wow, thanks! | 给我的？哇哦，谢谢！",
          "4": "This isn't very fun...$s | 这个没什么意思……$s",
          "6": "Yuck, what is this?$s | 呃，这是什么？$s",
          "8": "Thanks! | 谢谢！"
        },
        "Haley": {
          "0": "Oh my god, this is my favorite thing!! | 天哪，这是我的最爱！！",
          "2": "*gasp*...for me? Thank you! | *喘气*……给我的？非常感谢！",
          "4": "Ugh...that's such a stupid gift. | 呃……真是件蠢礼物。",
          "6": "Gross! | 恶心！",
          "8": "Thank you. I love presents. | 谢谢。我喜欢礼物。"
        },
        "Linus": {
          "0": "This is wonderful! You've really made my day special. | 这份礼物真是太棒了！我这一天因为你变得格外特别。",
          "2": "This is a great gift. Thank you! | 这礼物真不错。非常感谢！",
          "4": "Hmm... This doesn't really do much for me. | 唔……这个对我来说没什么用。",
          "6": "Why would you give this to me? Do you think I like junk just because I live in a tent? That's terrible. | 你为什么要给我这个？我住在帐篷里所以你觉得我喜欢垃圾吗？真差劲。",
          "8": "A gift? How nice. | 礼物？真好啊。"
        },
        "Gus": {
          "0": "You're giving this... to me? I'm speechless. | 你把这个送给我？我开心得不知道说什么了。",
          "2": "Oh, goodness! Are you sure? | 噢，天哪！你真的送给我？",
          "4": "No, no, no... | 不，不，不……",
          "6": "This is absolute junk. I'm offended. | 这完全是垃圾。你冒犯到我了。",
          "8": "Oh, that's sweet. Thank you. | 噢，这个不错。谢谢。"
        },
        "Robin": {
          "0": "This is for me? Wow, I absolutely love it!! | 这是给我的吗？哇哦，我爱死它了！！",
          "2": "Thanks! This is really nice! | 谢谢！我很喜欢！",
          "4": "Um... why? | 呃……为什么给我这个？",
          "6": "What the...? This is terrible! | 怎么回事……？这礼物太糟糕了！",
          "8": "Thank you. This might come in handy. | 谢谢。这个我也许用得着。"
        },
        "George": {
          "0": "This is my favorite thing! Thank you. | 这是我最喜欢的东西！谢谢。",
          "2": "Thanks. | 谢谢你啊。",
          "4": "That's a terrible gift. | 真是个糟糕的礼物。",
          "6": "This is probably the worst gift I've ever seen. Thanks a lot. | 这是我见过最烂的礼物了。多谢。",
          "8": "A gift? Hmm...#$e#Do you want something in return? | 礼物？唔……#$e#你想要什么回礼吗？"
