        "Universal_Love": {
          "0": "74 446 797 373 279 | 74 446 797 373 279"
        },
        "Leo": {
          "0": "I love this. I'm going to put it in my nest. | 我超喜欢的。我要把它放进窝里。",
          "2": "Are you sure? This is so nice... | 真的是给我的吗？太棒了……",
          "4": "Oh... I don't know if I can digest this... | 啊……不知道这个我能不能消化……",
          "6": "*sniff* *sniff*... Why are you giving this to me? Do you want me to bury it for you? | （嗅嗅）……为什么要给我这个？你想让我帮你把它埋起来吗？",
          "8": "I accept your gift. | 我接受你的礼物。"
