        },
        "Penny": {
          "0": "Thank you! I really love this! | 非常感谢！我太喜欢这个了！",
          "2": "Thank you! This looks special. | 非常感谢！这看起来很特别。",
          "4": "Uh, it's for me? ...Thanks. | 呃，给我的？……谢谢。",
          "6": "Ugh...I'm sorry, but I absolutely hate this. | 啊……抱歉，但是我真的很讨厌这个。",
          "8": "Thanks, this looks nice. | 谢谢，这看起来不错。"
        },
        "Kent": {
          "0": "Oh...! Mom used to give me this when I was a young boy. It brings back wonderful memories. Thank you. | 噢……！我小时候妈妈经常给我这个。这让我回想起那段美好的时光。谢谢。",
          "2": "Hey, now this is a really great gift. Thanks. | 嘿，这真是个不错的礼物。谢谢你啊。",
          "4": "Ah... It's a... what is this, exactly? Hmm... | 啊……啊……这是个……这到底是什么？嗯……唔……",
          "6": "This... They gave this to me in Gotoro prison camp. I've been trying to forget about that. *shudder* | 这个……在戈特洛集中营他们给过我这个。我一直试图忘了这件事。*发抖*",
          "8": "That's kind of you. The family will like this. | 你人真好。家里人会喜欢的。"
        },
        "Abigail": {
          "0": "I seriously love this! You're the best, @! | 我真的很喜欢这个！你是最棒的，@！",
          "2": "Hey, how'd you know I was hungry? This looks delicious! | 嘿，你怎么知道我饿了的？这个看起来好好吃！",
          "4": "What am I supposed to do with this? | 我能用这个干嘛？",
          "6": "What were you thinking? This is awful! | 你在想什么？真差劲！",
          "8": "You brought me a present? Thanks. | 你给我带了礼物？谢谢你啊。"
        },
        "Sebastian": {
          "0": "I really love this. How did you know? | 我真的很喜欢这东西。你怎么会知道的？",
          "2": "Thanks, I like this. | 谢谢，我喜欢这个。",
          "4": "...? | ……？",
          "6": "...I hate this. | ……我讨厌这个。",
          "8": "...thanks. | ……谢谢。"
