        "Sandy": {
          "0": "Ooo! I absolutely love getting gifts from the valley. I'm so happy!~ | 噢！我真的超喜欢收到来自镇里的礼物。我太开心了！~",
          "2": "This looks wonderful. Thanks so much! | 看起来很棒。太谢谢啦！",
