          "8": "This is for me? Thank you! | 这是给我的吗？非常感谢！"
        },
        "Alex": {
          "0": "Hey, awesome! I love this stuff! | 嘿，真棒！我超爱这个！",
          "2": "This is cool! Thanks. | 这东西好酷！谢谢你啊。",
