          "0": "This is my all-time favorite! Thank you! | 我最喜欢这个了！非常感谢！",
          "2": "That's very kind of you. I like this. | 你人真好。我喜欢这个。",
          "4": "This isn't exactly my favorite... | 这可不是我的最爱……",
          "6": "Please, never bring this to me again. | 拜托，再也别把这个带给我了。",
          "8": "A present? Thanks! | 礼物？谢谢！"
        },
        "Caroline": {
          "0": "Oh, @... you're spoiling me! I love it! | 你把这个送给我？我开心得不知道说什么了。",
          "2": "For me? This is such a thoughtful gift! Thank you! | 噢，天哪！你真的送给我？",
          "4": "Oh... I see. I'll, uh... make sure to put it to good use... | 不，不，不……",
          "6": "Um... I guess I could use it for compost... | 这完全是垃圾。我感觉被侮辱了。",
          "8": "Oh, that's sweet. Thank you. | 噢，这个不错。谢谢。"
        }
      }
