        "Shop_Pierre": "Psst... I'm selling eggs for cash! Hehe... Don't tell Lewis. / 嘘……我这可以用现金买三花蛋！嘿嘿……别跟刘易斯说啊。",
        "Jas_IceCream": "Is... Is that for me?$u#$b#Wow! This exactly what I wanted... Thank you! You're so nice!$h / 这……这是给我的吗？$u#$b#哇！我正好想要这个……谢谢你！你人真好！$h",
