        "DesertFestival_Maru_marriage": "How's the Calico Egg collection coming along? There's so many cool prizes!$h#$e#I know you'll do great. / 你的卡利科三花蛋收集得怎么样？有好多精美的奖品！$h#$e#我相信你能搞定的。",
