        "MakeOver_Emily_Done": "So? What do you think?#$b#I've put your old clothes in your backpack in case you change your mind!$h / 嗯？感觉怎么样？#$b#假如你想换回旧衣服也没事，我放在你背包里了！$h",
        "FishFrenzy_town": "{1} {0} frenzy has begun in town. / 镇上掀起了{0}狂潮。",
