        "bigtree": "It's a big tree, but the wood is starting to rot... / 这是一棵大树，但木头已经开始腐烂了……",
        "QiSummitCheat": "Well, well, well... Look who 'made it' to the summit.#$b#Thought you were really clever, didn't you?#$b#'How can I cheat the system for my own benefit?', you thought.#$b#Or, in layman's terms: 'Me me me me me me me me me me me me me me me me'.#$b#Despicable. / 哟呵……山顶冒出了一位贵客呀。#$b#你是不是觉得自己特聪明？#$b#你肯定在想，作个弊看看有什么好东西吧。#$b#你这种人，眼里只有你自己。#$b#真是卑鄙。",
