        "JojaCatalogueDescription": "Grants one (1) lifetime subscription to the Official Joja THRIVE Collection, featuring 40 exclusive furniture pieces! / 可获得 Joja 官方“拥抱成功”套装的 1 份终身订阅，包含 40 款独家家具！",
        "DF_Mine_Explanation": "---Welcome to the Skull Cavern Challenge!--- / ——欢迎参加骷髅洞穴挑战！——^^Calico Eggs and mysterious Calico Statues have appeared throughout the caverns.^ / ^洞穴各处出现了卡利科三花蛋和神秘的卡利科三花雕像。^",
