        "Farm_Ranching_Description": "Meadowlands Farm_It's not the best for growing crops, but there's a chewy blue grass that animals love. You start with two chickens. / 草原农场_不是种植作物的最佳去处，但是长有耐嚼的蓝色草，动物们很喜欢。开始时拥有两只鸡。",
