        "Cook_Sauce0": "Rich Marinara / 番茄罗勒酱",
        "SquidFest_GotAllRewardsToday": "Congratulations! You hit our iridium-level target and earned all possible rewards for today. / 恭喜！你达到了我们的铱星目标，赢得了今天所有的奖励。",
        "DF_Mine_CalicoStatue_Description_11": "Full refresh! / 完全恢复！",
