        "PerfectIceRod": "Perfect Ice Rod / 完美冰霜法杖",
        "Shop_Leo": "Can I have some eggs? I want to put them in my nest. / 能给我一些三花蛋吗？我想放到我的窝里。",
        "frog_variant_3": "Blue Frog Egg / 蓝蛙蛋",
        "Shady_Guy_Ongoing": "Suspicious Guy: Eyes on the race, kid! We can talk later... / 可疑的家伙：${小子^小姑娘}$，现在专注看比赛！之后再聊……",
        "DesertFestival_Abigail": "I'm glad you fixed up the bus! This is really fun.$h#$e#I've always wanted to travel beyond Pelican Town. / 谢谢你修好了巴士！坐巴士很快乐。$h#$e#我一直想去鹈鹕镇外面旅行。",
        "forester_profession_possible": "Mushroom logs and boxes have a {0}% chance to produce double. / 蘑菇树桩和箱子的产量有 {0}% 的几率翻倍。",
        "BlessingOfWaters_description": "The first three fish you hook today will be much easier. ({0} left) / 你今天钓前三条鱼时会更轻松。（还有 {0} 条）",
        "Scholar_Question_3_1_Answers": "Mullner,Millener,Molnar,Nelson,Miller / 莫尔纳,米勒纳,凡尔纳,尼尔森,瓦尔纳",
        "DesertFestival_Jodi": "Oh, don't mind me, I'm just doing a little shopping.#$e#If I don't browse the shops, I might miss the perfect decoration for our living room! / 啊，不用管我，我就买点东西。#$e#我在找最适合家里客厅的装饰品，要是不好好逛商店可能会错过！",
        "Cook_DishNames_2_3": "Warrior Smoothie / 勇士奶昔",
