        "BlessingOfTheButterfly": "Blessing Of The Butterfly / 蝴蝶祝福",
        "DF_Mine_CalicoStatue_Description_2": "Skeletons are after you... / 骷髅在追杀你……",
        "SquidFestBooth_Intro": "Welcome to SquidFest! What can I do for you? / 欢迎来到鱿鱼节！您有什么事？",
        "QoS_Cookbook": "You learned {0} new recipes. / 你学习了 {0} 个新食谱。",
        "MakeOver_Emily_InventoryFull": "Hmm, your backpack's looking a little full. Come back when you've made enough room for a full set of clothes! / 唔，你的背包好像有点满。等你腾出一整套衣服的空间再来吧！",
        "CactusMan_Intro_1": "Cactus Man: Ah, yes... You look like someone who would appreciate what I'm offering. / 仙人掌商人：很好……你看起来会喜欢我给你的东西。",
        "DesertFestival_Kent": "Hey, @. Enjoying the heat? / 哎，@，你喜欢这种炎热的天气吗？",
        "Cook_Intro_No": "Chef: Pity. Come back when you're ready for something delicious. / 厨师：真遗憾，等你准备好吃顿大餐的时候再回来吧。",
        "CactusMan_Question": "Cactus Man: Are you ready to welcome a new cactus into your life? / 仙人掌商人：你准备好迎接一株新的仙人掌的到来了吗？",
        "FairyBox_Description2": "Summons a level {0} fairy companion that heals you in combat situations. / 召唤一个跟随你的 {0} 级仙女，战斗时提供治疗。",
        "DesertFestival_Caroline": "This weather is just perfect. I can't tell where my skin ends and the air begins.$h / 天气真是太好了，我感觉要融化在空气里了。$h",
        "DesertFestival_Evelyn": "Ah... the sands of time, the sands of time... / 啊……时间就像流沙……",
        "FishingDerby_Exclamation2": "It got away... / 逃走了……",
        "DesertFestival_Shane_marriage": "Remind me to brush my teeth tonight... there's twelve unique soda flavors, and I'm on track to try them all.#$e#Mmm... cave carrot soda... *slurp* / 今晚记得提醒我刷牙……有十二种口味的汽水，我打算全部尝一遍。#$e#唔……山洞胡萝卜汽水……（咕嘟咕嘟）",
        "MasteryRequirement": "You don't yet have the knowledge to use this... / 你掌握的知识不足，无法使用这个……",
        "GameMenu_Animals": "Animals / 动物",
        "SquidFest_NowOpen": "SquidFest has begun. / 鱿鱼节开始了。",
        "Scholar_Question_3_1": "Question 4: What is George's last name? / 问题 4：乔治姓什么？",
        "Trinkets_Description": "Unlocks a new equipment slot for trinkets. Trinkets can be found while adventuring and grant special powers. / 解锁了一个新的饰品装备栏。饰品会赋予特殊能力，在探险时可以找到。",
        "Shop_Emily": "Ah, it feels good here in the shade. / 啊，在阴凉的地方感觉真舒服。",
        "Shop_Elliott": "Some interesting things washed up on the beach. Care to trade? / 我在海滩上捡到了一些有趣的东西，要不要交换？",
        "BlessingOfLuck": "Blessing Of Luck / 幸运祝福",
        "FirstCatch": "First Catch! / 第一次钓到！",
        "DesertFestival_Vincent": "Mom, I'm bored! / 妈妈，我好无聊！",
        "Cook_Intro_Yes": "Chef: Ooh, yes... I'm very pleased to hear that. *slurp* / 厨师：哇……那实在太好了。（咂嘴）",
        "Shop_Kent": "Hey, I've got a few things for sale. Let me know if anything catches your eye. / 哎，我有几样东西要卖，你看看有没有感兴趣的。",
        "DF_Mine_CalicoStatue_Description_3": "More Bats / 蝙蝠增多",
        "Race_Comment_2": "It was neck-and-neck! / 简直是并驾齐驱！",
        "Willy_Challenge_Description_1": "Willy has challenged you to catch 3 Sandfish. / 威利提出挑战，要你钓 3 条沙鱼。",
        "MakeOver_Sandy_6": "That was fun!$h#$b#I hope you're as happy with your new look as I am!$h / 真开心！$h#$b#我觉得你的新穿搭很好看，希望你也喜欢！$h",
        "JojaCatalogueDescriptionTerms": "Terms Of Service: / 服务条款：^^By activating this item, the user hereby agrees not to hold Joja Co. responsible for any damage to life or property resulting from the use of Joja THRIVE Furniture.^^The user is aware that there may be untested plastic materials present in one or more THRIVE furniture pieces, and waives any right to hold Joja Co. liable for adverse health outcomes attributable to contact with said plastic materials.^^The user hereby waives any right to hold Joja Co. liable for so-called \"shoddy workmanship\", and agrees that any and all bodily harm resulting from breakage, cracking, powdering, bending, clamping, pinching, impaling, or any other unintended effect of using Joja THRIVE Furniture, is solely the result of voluntary user action.^^   --Join us. Thrive.-- / ^用户激活此物品即视为同意，使用 Joja“拥抱成功”家具如果造成人身或财产损害，Joja 公司不承担任何责任。^^用户理解并同意，“拥抱成功”家具中可能包含未经测试的塑料材料，如果因接触上述塑料材料造成不良健康后果，Joja 公司不承担任何责任。^^用户理解并同意，Joja 公司对所谓“劣质工艺”不承担任何责任，使用 Joja“拥抱成功”家具时如果因为破损、开裂、粉末化、弯曲、被夹、挤压、刺穿或任何其他意外情况造成人身伤害，属于用户自愿行为，后果由用户自行承担。^^   ——加入我们 拥抱成功——",
        "DesertFestival_Shane": "I came here once when I was a kid... The only thing I remember is getting sick on the bus ride. / 我小时候来过一次……我就记得坐巴士的时候晕车了。",
        "MagicHairDye_Description": "Your hair shimmers with all the colors of a prismatic shard. / 你的头发闪烁着五彩碎片的所有颜色。",
        "DesertFestival_Linus": "I hitched a ride underneath the bus.#$e#You can't find this Calico Desert flavor anywhere else. Heheh...$h / 我搭了个顺风车，不过是扒在巴士的车底下。#$e#满满的卡利科沙漠风味，独此一家。嘿嘿……$h",
        "MannequinFemale_Name": "Mannequin (F) / 假人模特（女）",
        "ChooseOne": "Choose One: / 选择一个：",
        "MakeOver_Emily_Reaction8": "Here, let me use my finger to smudge this a bit... / 这里用手抹开一点……",
        "MakeOver_Emily_Reaction9": "Okay, get ready, this might be a tight fit... / 这里可能有点紧，准备一下……",
        "SkillBookMessage": "You've learned a few things about {0}. / 你学到了一些{0}方面的知识。",
        "FishingDerbyBooth_BagFull": "Looks like your bag's full. Better make some room first. / 你的包好像满了，先腾出点空间吧。",
        "Renovation_AddExtendedCornerRoom": "Expand Corner Room/Extends the corner room, adding a large new area./Select an area for the renovation. / 扩大角落房间/将角落房间扩建成一片宽敞的空间。/选择装修区域。",
        "tapper_profession_possible": "+1 tapper output per harvest. / 树液采集器每次产量 +1。",
        "MakeOver_Emily_5": "Yes! I can feel it, your inner self and outer self are now in perfect alignment!$h#$b#I can't wait for you to see the new 'you'!$h / 不错！我能感觉到，你的内在和外在已经完全一致了！$h#$b#快来看看全新的自己吧！$h",
        "TroutDerby_NowOpen": "The Annual Trout Derby has begun. / 一年一度的鳟鱼大赛开始了。",
        "CactusMan_Closed": "Cactus Man: They're feeling shy right now. Come back later. / 仙人掌商人：它们现在有点害羞，晚点再来吧。",
        "Marlon_4": "I can see a bold look in your eye.#$b#How about a challenge? / 你眼中闪烁着勇气的光芒。#$b#要不要来一场挑战？",
        "BlessingOfFriendship_description": "You gain extra friendship from speaking to people. / 你与人交谈时可以增进更多友谊。",
        "Shop_Sam": "Want my old broken skateboard? I guess you could use it for decoration or something. / 我的破滑板你要吗？说不定可以用来当装饰。",
        "Shady_Guy_Ended": "Suspicious Guy: It's too late, kid. Come back when the races are happening. / 可疑的家伙：${小子^小姑娘}$，你来晚了，有比赛的时候再来。",
        "DF_Mine_CalicoStatue": "Calico Statue / 卡利科三花雕像",
        "DF_Mine_CalicoStatue_Description_4": "Bugs become Assassin Bugs / 臭虫变成了刺客臭虫",
        "Claim": "Claim / 领取",
        "Shady_Guy_Closed": "Suspicious Guy: Heh... not now, kid. Come back later, and we can talk. / 可疑的家伙：呃……${小子^小姑娘}$，现在不方便，你晚点再来找我。",
        "Race_Winner": "This race's winner is... / 这次比赛的冠军是……",
        "Marlon_1": "Looking to test your mettle, huh?#$b#I've got a few challenges that might do just that. / 怎么，想要测试你的勇气？#$b#我这有几个挑战可以满足你的要求。",
        "Scholar_Question_0_0_Answers": "Clint,Gunther,Gus,Willy,Marnie,Pierre,Robin,Marlon / 克林特,冈瑟,格斯,威利,玛妮,皮埃尔,罗宾,马龙",
        "MakeOver_Sandy_2": "Oops! That's my cue! / 哎呀！该我上了！",
        "buy_books": "Buy Books / 购买书籍",
        "DF_Mine_CalicoStatue_Description_8": "Monsters do more damage / 怪物造成的伤害增加",
        "Shady_Guy_Selected_3": "Suspicious Guy: {0}? Sure, sure... Good luck, kid.  / 可疑的家伙：要选{0}？没问题，没问题……${小子^小姑娘}$，祝你好运。",
        "Raccoon_expanded": "The raccoon shop has been expanded. / 浣熊商店现已扩建。",
        "MakeOver_Sandy_InventoryFull": "Hmm, your backpack's looking a little full. Come back when you've made enough room for a full set of clothes. / 唔，你的背包好像有点满。等你腾出一整套衣服的空间再来吧。",
        "DwarfStatue_1": "Greater chance to find ladders and shafts. / 找到梯子和竖井的几率更高。",
        "Cook_DishNames_1_4": "Hot Log / 木头热狗",
        "Race_Go": "GO! / 开始！",
        "CactusMan_Yes_1": "Cactus Man: Yes, he bears a striking resemblance to you, don't you agree? / 仙人掌商人：嗯，它和你长得实在太像了，你不觉得吗？",
        "Shop_Leah": "I had some extra wood, so I made these mini bookcases... / 我手里多了一些木板，所以做了这些迷你书架……",
        "Spouse_Goodnight0": "Goodnight, {0}. / 晚安，{0}。",
        "ParrotEgg_Description": "Summons a level {0} parrot companion, who grants you a {1} chance to find gold coins when slaying monsters. / 召唤一只跟随你的 {0} 级鹦鹉，使得杀怪时有{1}概率掉落金币。",
        "Renovation_RemoveCubby": "Remove Cubby/Removes the little cubby next to the front door./Select an area for the renovation. / 拆除凹间/拆除大门旁边的小凹间。/选择装修区域。",
        "Trinkets": "Trinkets: / 饰品：",
        "MasteryHint": "You sense that a new way is open... / 你感觉到有新的道路开启了……",
        "Cook_Ingredient3": "Extremely Sharp Cheddar / 陈年切达奶酪",
        "DesertFestival_George": "What is she mumbling about? I'm here for the spicy food tent! / 她在嘀咕什么？我就想去那个帐篷吃点辣的东西！",
        "SlimeGathererEnchantment": "Slime Gatherer / 史莱姆刮泥",
        "CursedMannequin_Description": "You can dress it up however you like. And pray that it doesn't come to life while you sleep... / 可以随意打扮它。记得祈祷它不会在你睡觉的时候活过来……",
        "Raccoon_interim_4": "Raccoon: You're a good friend, bobo. Now we can have another... / 浣熊：波波，你真是我的好朋友。我们家可以再有一个了……",
        "Raccoon_receive": "Raccoon: Thanks, bobo. Take this... / 浣熊：波波，谢谢你。给你这个……",
        "Cook_DishNames_2_1": "Superfood Cake / 健康食品蛋糕",
        "WizardCatalogueLetter": "My ex-wife took all the furniture. / 我的前妻把所有家具都拿走了。^^Fortunately, I had the good sense to make ethereal copies of everything and transcribe them into this book. Enjoy.^^-M. Rasmodius / ^幸亏我有先见之明，把所有东西做了幻影备份，收录在这本书里了。希望你喜欢。^^——M·拉斯莫迪斯",
        "frog_variant_6": "Void Frog Egg / 虚空蛙蛋",
        "Cook_Sauce4": "Uncomfortably Hot Sauce / 魔鬼辣酱",
        "SquidFestSign": "[textcolor black][letterbg LooseSprites\\\\squidFestLetterBG 0]             -----SquidFest----- / [textcolor black][letterbg LooseSprites\\\\squidFestLetterBG 0]             ——— 鱿鱼节 ———^^Friday the 12th and Saturday the 13th.^^A two-day squid fishing bonanza. If you can reach our daily catch targets, you'll win prizes.^^(Note: Any personal items found near this sign will be sent to the lost and found) / ^12 日（星期五）至 13 日（星期六）。^^为期两天的鱿鱼钓鱼盛宴。如果你能达到我们的每日钓鱼目标，就可以赢得奖品。^^（注意：在此标志附近发现的个人物品将送至失物招领处）",
        "Shady_Guy_Intro": "Suspicious Guy: Psst... Hey, kid. You been watching these races? Pretty exciting, huh? / 可疑的家伙：喂，${小子^小姑娘}$，你看比赛了没？刺不刺激？",
        "MakeOver_Emily_AlreadyStyled": "You're looking great!$h#$b#Come back another day and we'll put together a fresh new look for you! / 你看起来很漂亮啊！$h#$b#改天再来，我们到时候给你准备一套全新的穿搭！",
        "DF_Mine_CalicoStatue_Name_0": "Ghost Invasion / 幽灵来袭",
        "FishingDerbyBooth_NoTags": "Seems like you don't have any Golden Tags... better get fishing! / 你好像没有黄金标签……赶紧开始钓鱼吧！",
        "Scholar_Question_3_2_Answers": "8,12,6,11,4,10 / 8,12,6,11,4,10",
        "DesertFestival_Elliott_marriage": "Well well well, what have we here? A beautiful desert rose!$h#$e#Make sure to stay watered, dear. / 哎呦喂，快来看！好漂亮的沙漠玫瑰！$h#$e#亲爱的，记得保持水分哦。",
        "DesertFestival_Abigail_marriage": "I was thinking of joining you in the skull caves, but then I saw the food stand...#$e#You go on ahead without me... just be careful! / 我本来想跟你一起去骷髅洞穴，但是现在看到了那边的小吃摊……#$e#你先走吧，不用等我……路上小心点！",
        "Renovation_AddCubby": "Add Cubby/Adds a little cubby next to the front door./Select an area for the renovation. / 修建凹间/在大门旁边增加一个小凹间。/选择装修区域。",
        "SkillName_2": "Foraging / 采集",
        "Foraging_Mastery": "You now find Golden Mystery Boxes, which contain superior items. / 你可以找到金色谜之盒了，里面装有优质物品。",
        "FishingDerbyBooth_Explanation": "During this event, Rainbow Trout have a chance of carrying a 'Golden Tag'. If you find one, turn it in here for a prize! / 在此活动期间，彩虹鳟鱼有几率藏有“黄金标签”，如果找到了可以拿过来获取奖励！",
        "Anvil_fail": "You can only re-forge trinkets on this. / 这里只能重新锻造饰品。",
        "Raccoon_intro_0": "Raccoon: Hungry... need fish... / 浣熊：饿了……想吃鱼……",
        "Anvil_wrongtrinket": "This trinket cannot be re-forged. / 这个饰品无法重新锻造。",
        "Scholar_Question_0_2_Answers": "Calico Desert,Carlito Desert,Conical Desert,Caprico Desert,Canonical Desert,Cowlicko Desert,Catacomb Desert,Capicola Desert,Skull Cavern Desert / 卡利科沙漠,科利卡沙漠,卡科利沙漠,利科卡沙漠,科卡利沙漠,利卡科沙漠,卡塔科沙漠,卡拉科沙漠,骷髅洞穴沙漠",
        "TravelingMerchant_DF": "Ahh... nothing like the warm air of Calico Desert. The pig loves it, too. / 啊……卡利科沙漠的暖风最舒服了，小猪也很喜欢。",
        "Renovation_AddAttic": "Add Attic/Adds another staircase up, and a room at the top./Select an area for the renovation. / 修建阁楼/增加一处楼梯，通向顶部的房间。/选择装修区域。",
        "DesertFestival_Lewis2": "All of this is possible because you fixed the bus, @! I can't thank you enough. / @，能来这里都是多亏你修好了巴士！实在太感谢你了。",
        "Scholar_Question_1_0_Answers": "Spring,Summer,Fall / 春季,夏季,秋季",
        "DF_Mine_CalicoStatue_Description_14": "Monsters do less damage / 怪物造成的伤害减少",
        "FairyBox_Description": "Summons a fairy companion that heals you in combat situations. / 召唤一个跟随你的仙女，战斗时提供治疗。",
        "DesertFestival_Penny_marriage": "Hi, honey. I'm just browsing to see if there's anything nice for the house.$h / 亲爱的，我就随便看看有没有适合买回家的东西。$h",
        "Shady_Guy_Late": "Suspicious Guy: Too late, the race's started. Let's talk again later... / 可疑的家伙：太晚了，比赛已经开始了。等会儿再聊……",
        "Marlon_Challenge_Finished_LastDay": "Hey, you did it! I'm impressed.#$b#That's it for this year, but Gil and I will be here again next time around. / 哇，你成功了！很了不起。#$b#今年的活动就到这里，我和吉尔下次还会来的。",
        "DesertFestival_Pierre": "As a shopkeeper, I find it interesting to see how other people run their shops.#$e#*whisper* Don't tell Sandy, but my grocery selection blows hers out of the water! / 我觉得观察其他人开店很有意思，毕竟我也是店主。#$e#（悄悄地）我店里的货比桑迪的强太多了！别告诉她啊。",
        "Cook_DishNames_1_2": "Crystal Cake / 水晶蛋糕",
        "Cook_DishNames_2_0": "Sour Salad / 酸味沙拉",
        "Scholar_Wrong": "Scholar: Wrong! ...I'm sorry, friend. But you will have to come back another time. / 学者：错了！……朋友，很抱歉，你只能下次再来了。",
        "DF_Mine_CalicoStatue_Description_7": "More monsters / 怪物增多",
        "MakeOver_Emily_Reaction7": "Let's trim this a little here... / 这里要稍微裁短一点……",
        "windstorm": "There was a strong wind storm during the night... / 昨晚刮了一场大风……",
        "CactusMan_Intro_2": "Cactus Man: Oh, yes... I've got the perfect match for you. / 仙人掌商人：嗯……我正好有最适合你的那个。",
        "FixRaccoonStump_Done": "Maybe someone will decide to move in... / 或许会有谁决定搬进来……",
        "DesertFestival_Alex_marriage": "Hey... you look really cute in the desert sun...$h / 哎……你在沙漠的阳光下看起来真可爱……$h",
        "Scholar_Question_2_2_Answers": "800g,1500g,16000g,8000g,1200g,11000g,7500g / 800 金,1500 金,16000 金,8000 金,1200 金,11000 金,7500 金",
        "DF_Mine_CalicoStatue_Name_1": "Serpent Invasion / 飞蛇来袭",
        "DesertFestival_Emily2_marriage": "I've been having fun, but I'm so busy I haven't been able to do any chores at home. I hope you're doing okay! / 我玩得很开心，但是太忙了，还没来得及做家务。你也开心点！",
        "books_trade_welcome": "I'll trade useful stuff for your extra books. / 你可以用多余的书来换有用的东西。",
        "Race_Comment_3": "Such speed has rarely been seen! / 这样的速度实属罕见！",
        "MakeOver_NoStylist": "Please return when an attendant is present. / 请等有工作人员在场时再来。",
        "IridiumSpur_Description": "Critical strikes give you a speed boost for {0} seconds. / 暴击时，获得 {0} 秒加速。",
        "Race_Guess_Made": "Race Announcer: {0}? Okay. Now sit back and enjoy the race! / 比赛播报员：你选{0}？好的。现在坐下来欣赏比赛吧！",
        "MakeOver_Sandy_4": "Let's see here... / 我来看看……",
        "MakeOver_Emily_4": "There! / 完成了！",
        "Shady_Guy_Intro_3": "Suspicious Guy: Just pick a racer, and their next race will be a real stinker... catch my drift? / 可疑的家伙：你选一个参赛选手，它下场比赛保准会栽个大跟头……懂我意思不？",
        "CactusMan_Collected": "Cactus Man: So, how's the little guy doing? / 仙人掌商人：小家伙怎么样了？",
        "frog_variant_5": "Yellow Frog Egg / 黄蛙蛋",
        "Scholar_Intro": "Scholar: Greetings, friend! Care for a test of knowledge? If you can answer my questions correctly, you'll earn a prize. What do you say? / 学者：朋友，你好！想来一次知识测试吗？如果你能正确回答我的问题，我就给你奖品，怎么样？",
        "DesertFestival_Leah": "I was just wondering... If I lived here, instead of Stardew Valley, would my art look different? / 我在想……假如我没有住在星露谷而是住在这里，我会画出不一样的画吗？",
        "DesertFestival_Harvey_marriage": "Hey, @. I'll be working late during the festival, so don't wait up for me at night!#$e#Promise me you'll be careful in the skull caves. / @，因为节日我会工作到很晚，晚上就不用等我了！#$e#答应我，在骷髅洞穴里一定要小心。",
        "Cook_DishNames_0_3": "Skull Cave Casserole / 骷髅洞穴砂锅煲",
        "DF_Mine_CalicoStatue_Name_6": "Meager Meals / 粗茶淡饭",
        "Fizz_Intro_1": "So... you got my letter, huh? Nice to meet ya.#$b#I'm Fizz. Joja Special Services Division.$h#$b#You haven't heard of us? That's okay, most people haven't...#$b#We're not really advertised like other Joja products. We're more of a 'specialty service' for elite clients.#$b#What do we do? Heh... well, let's just say... we specialize in 'legally complex' matters... catch my drift?#$b#But enough chit chat. Let's get to business.#$b#I've heard you're trying to achieve 'perfection'. A noble goal! ... but difficult. Very difficult.#$b#All that cooking, crafting, monster slaying, all those complicated friendships... *groan*. I can see how stressed you are.$s#$b#But here's the thing... you don't need to stress another minute! We've got you covered.$h#$b#See these papers here? They're called 'perfection waivers'.#$b#Each one of these beautiful pages are worth 1% toward perfection. They've even got Mr. Qi's signature on it... completely legit!#$b#Do I look like someone who would lie to you??$u#$b#...$u#$b#Don't answer that.#$b#...Anyway, I'm selling these for a sweet, sweet price... just 500,000g a pop. A steal!#$b#Well, no pressure. Just think about it! I'll be waiting...$h / 哦……看来你收到我的信了？你好你好。#$b#我叫菲兹，来自 Joja 特别服务部门。$h#$b#你是不是没听说过我们？没关系，大多数人都不知道……#$b#我们不像其他Joja产品有很多广告宣传。我们更像是为精英客户提供的“特别服务”。#$b#我们是干什么的呢？呵呵……这样说吧……我们专门处理“原则上很复杂”的事情……懂我意思不？#$b#闲聊也够了，我们谈正事吧。#$b#我听说你正在努力实现“完美”，多么伟大的目标！……但是很困难。极其困难。#$b#要做各种烹饪、打造、杀怪，还有复杂的交友……嚯！你压力不大就怪了。$s#$b#不过听好了……你的困难在我这里就迎刃而解了！我们可以轻松搞定。$h#$b#看到这些文件了吗？这是《完美豁免书》。#$b#每一张都代表了 1% 的完美度，多么美妙！而且还有齐先生的亲笔签名……绝对正版！#$b#我看起来像个骗子吗？？$u#$b#……$u#$b#谁让你回答了。#$b#……总之，我可以卖给你这种文件，价格非常诱人……每张只要 500,000 金。简直是白菜价！#$b#没事，不急的，你好好考虑一下！我等着你来……$h",
        "Cook_Done": "Chef: Voila. I call it, '{0}'. Enjoy! / 厨师：做好啦！名字就叫，“{0}”。请享用！",
        "Mining_Mastery": "Gem-bearing rocks now grant twice the gems. / 产宝石的岩石产量翻倍了。",
        "HeavyMagicQuiver": "Heavy Magic Quiver / 重型魔法箭筒",
        "StarterChicken_Names": "Portobello,Porcini | Chicky,Grushenka | Lucky,Clover | Salt,Pepper | Pecky,Clucky | Brunhilde,Gretchen | Billie,Bertha | Pickle,Zucchini | Peachie,Papaya | Potpourri,Ann | Buster,Scrappy | Petal,Twig | Cheeper,Squeaks | Skwash,Pumpkin | Goldie,Cocoa | Toast,Beans | Chip,Dip | Hazel,Peanut | Winky,Nod | Huffy,Puffy | Eggy,Ollie | Polka,Dot | Tiny,Shrimp | Fishy,Roe | Princess,Lady | Misty,Beluga | Snowy,Gingersnap | Honey,Biscuit | Piccolo,Viola | Potatoes,Gravy / 小白,小棕 | 叽叽,喳喳 | 小银,小金 | 雪梨,苹果 | 草莓,黑莓 | 西瓜,芒果 | 玫瑰,樱花 | 小草,小茶 | 红豆,蛋挞 | 葡萄,椰子 | 太阳,月亮",
        "DF_Mine_CalicoStatue_Description_12": "50 Calico Eggs / 50 个卡利科三花蛋",
        "Tent_Blocked": "Needs more space to deploy. / 需要更多空间才能放置。",
        "Gil_Rating_10to14": "{0}, huh? Not bad, not bad... of course, when I was your age I was doin' twice that. With a Rusty Sword, and no food! / {0} 分？不错，不错……哎，我年轻的时候分数是你的两倍呢，就凭一把生锈的剑，还不吃东西！",
        "Mannequin_Description": "You can dress it up however you like. / 可以随意打扮它。",
        "SquidFestBooth_Explanation": "It's a squid fishing challenge! If you can hit our daily catch targets, you'll win prizes. Check the sign to the left. We also put special bait in the water so the squid are active all day! / 这是一场鱿鱼钓鱼挑战！如果你能达到我们的每日钓鱼目标，就可以赢得奖品。请查看左侧的告示牌。我们还在水里放了特殊的鱼饵，让鱿鱼全天都出来活动！",
        "Cook_DishNames_3_4": "Nachos Of The Desert / 沙漠玉米片",
        "BroccoliFusilli_Name": "Broccoli Fusilli / 西蓝花螺旋粉",
        "Gil_NextYear": "That's it for this year... *snore*... / 今年的活动到此为止……呼噜……",
        "DF_Mine_CalicoStatue_Name_5": "Thin Shells / 易碎蛋壳",
        "MakeOver_Sandy_5": "Okay! / 好了！",
        "RiverlandsFarmPerk": "You start with a Fish Smoker. / 开始时有一台熏鱼机。",
        "GoldClock_Off": "Turn the Golden Clock off? / 要关掉黄金时钟吗？",
        "ItemDeliveryQuestTitle": "Delivery: {0} / 送货：{0}",
        "RapidMagicQuiver": "Rapid Magic Quiver / 快速魔法箭筒",
        "FoundABook": "You found a copy of '{0}'. / 你找到了一本《{0}》。",
        "DesertFestival_Harvey": "Going into the caves can be really dangerous. I hope there are no accidents, but still... I'll be here all day just in case.#$e#As a doctor, I'd recommend minimizing your exposure to serpent-infested caverns! But ultimately, it's your choice. / 进入洞穴可能非常危险。我希望不要发生意外，不过……以防万一我还是待在这里吧。#$e#作为医生，我建议你尽量少接触满是飞蛇的洞穴！不过你硬要去我也拦不住你。",
        "DesertFestival_Haley2_marriage": "%Your wife is taking a nap. / %你的妻子在睡午觉。",
        "Shady_Guy_Question": "Suspicious Guy: Alright, so who's gonna be the unlucky racer? / 可疑的家伙：行了，你选哪个选手当倒霉蛋？",
        "DF_Mine_CalicoStatue_Description_6": "Food is half as effective / 食物的效果减半",
        "Leave": "Leave / 离开",
        "ParrotEgg_Name": "Parrot Egg / 鹦鹉蛋",
        "Racer_3": "Escar-go / 闪电蜗牛",
        "Renovation_RemoveExtendedCornerRoom": "Shrink Corner Room/Removes the expansion to the corner room, returning it to its original size./Select an area for the renovation. / 缩小角落房间/将角落房间恢复到原来的大小。/选择装修区域。",
        "guild_door": "Slay 1000 monsters to enter here. ([FarmerStat monstersKilled]/1000) / 杀死 1000 只怪物才能进入。（[FarmerStat monstersKilled]/1000）",
        "Gil_ComeBack": "That's it for today. You can try again tomorrow, if you're up for it... *snore*... / 今天就到此为止了，你要是想的话可以明天再试试……呼噜……",
        "Gil_Rating_1000": "You hear a voice in your head: 'It would be dishonorable to submit an egg rating acquired through the use of cheat code software!' / 你的脑海中响起一个声音：“用作弊软件修改三花蛋分数然后提交是可耻的！”",
        "ForestPylon": "A receptacle of unknown origins... / 来历不明的底座……",
        "Pam_busSign_resort": "I'm on vacation today! You'll have to drive yourself.       -Pam / 我今天去度假了！你自己开车吧。——潘姆",
        "Cook_DishNames_4_4": "Desert Gumbo / 沙漠秋葵汤",
        "Scholar_Intro2": "Scholar: Excellent! Now, for the first question... / 学者：太好了！来，请听第一个问题……",
        "JunimoCatalogueDescription": "A collection of furniture infused with Junimo energy. / 注入了祝尼魔能量的家具套装。",
        "DesertFestival_Haley": "If you smell something good, it's the coconut oil I rubbed all over my skin.#$b#I'm going 'all in' with the desert feeling!$h / 你是不是闻到香味了？是我在身上抹的椰子油。#$b#我要全力以赴体验沙漠风情！$h",
        "IridiumSpur": "IridiumSpur / IridiumSpur",
        "Shop_Jodi": "I'm sorry, my selection isn't very good this year... / 今年的货不是很好，不好意思……",
        "3_Mastery": "Mining Mastery / 采矿精通",
        "Scholar_Question_3_0_Options": "Stonefish,Ice Pip,Lava Eel / 石鱼,冰柱鱼,岩浆鳗鱼",
        "DesertFestival_Sandy": "This is probably the busiest time of the year for me! It's nice to be able to see everyone. / 这可能是我一年中最忙的时候了！能见到大家真好。",
        "Mayo_reaction1": "Did you just...? / 你刚才……？",
        "Cook_Ingredient2": "Rare Fruit / 稀有水果",
        "BearPaw_Description": "Blackberries and Salmonberries are worth 3x the gold. / 黑莓和美洲大树莓的售价提高到了原先的 3 倍。",
        "Cook_Sauce2": "Cherry Syrup / 樱桃糖浆",
        "Scholar_Question_1_1_Options": "Apricot,Peach,Pomegranate / 杏,桃,石榴",
        "Race_Closed": "Race Announcer: The racers need some time to prepare... Come back later! / 比赛播报员：选手们需要准备一会儿……稍后再来吧！",
        "Gil_NoRating": "It's a brand new day... come back when you've proven yourself in the caverns. / 新的一天开始了……等你在洞穴里面证明自己的实力之后再来吧。",
        "Pam_busSign": "I'm going to the festival today, kid! You'll have to drive yourself.       -Pam / 年轻人，我去参加节日了！你自己开车吧。——潘姆",
        "DF_Mine_Explanation_3": "...But be careful! The Calico Statues will also invoke various strange and dangerous effects! / ……但是要小心！卡利科三花雕像还会产生各种奇怪和危险的效果！^^Visit Gil to receive prizes for achieving a high \"Egg Rating\".^ / ^获得较高的“三花蛋分数”时，可以找吉尔领取奖励。^",
        "CritPowerEnchantment": "+{0} Crit. Power / +{0} 暴击威力",
        "DF_Mine_CalicoStatue_Name_15": "25 Egg Treasure / 25 个蛋礼包",
        "options_menubg_2": "None / 无",
        "DesertFestival_Leah_marriage": "I wanted to go swimming, but apparently the water's full of scorpion carp!$h / 我想去游泳，但水里面好像全是蝎鲤鱼！$h",
        "GreenRainForecast": "Um... There appears to be some kind of... anomalous reading... I... don't know what this means... / 呃……读数好像有点……异常……我……我不知道是什么意思……",
        "1_Mastery": "Fishing Mastery / 钓鱼精通",
        "MasteryCave": "Only a master of the five ways may enter. ({0}/5) / 只有精通五道的人才能进入。（{0}/5）",
        "DF_Mine_CalicoStatue_Description_0": "More Ghosts / 幽灵增多",
        "GiantQiFruitMessage": "Mr. Qi: Oh, you thought you could obtain my precious fruit whenever you like? Pshh... Only during the challenge, kid. / 齐先生：哈哈，你以为随时都能拿到我的珍贵水果吗？年轻人啊，很遗憾……只有挑战期间可以。",
        "Gil_Rating_1to4": "...{0}? Hahahaha.... okay, kiddo. Here's a little prizey for you... now, go along and play with the other kids. / ……{0} 分？哈哈哈哈……行了，孩子。给你一点小奖励……去找其他年轻人玩吧。",
        "CactusMan_Yes_Full": "Cactus Man: You don't have enough space... Come back after you've made some room. / 仙人掌商人：你的空间不够……腾出空间之后再来吧。",
        "Willy_Challenge_Description_3": "Willy has challenged you to find a \"Golden Bobber\". / 威利提出挑战，要你找到“黄金浮漂”。",
        "Scholar_Question_0_0_Options": "Blacksmith,Museum,Saloon,Fish Shop,Animal Shop,General Store / 铁匠铺,博物馆,酒吧,鱼店,动物商店,杂货店",
        "Raccoon_interim_5": "Raccoon: We're happy for now, bobo... / 浣熊：波波，我们现在很幸福了……",
        "MakeOver_Emily_Reaction4": "No... this won't do... / 不对……这样不行……",
        "MakeOver_Emily_Reaction6": "Oh look, a cauliflower fritter... / 这里怎么有个花椰菜饼……",
        "Cook_DishNames_3_0": "Calico Pizza / 卡利科披萨",
        "DwarfStatue_source": "Statue Of The Dwarf King / 矮人之王雕像",
        "DesertFestival_Demetrius": "Why do humans enjoy spicy food? It's counter-intuitive from a biological perspective.#$e#Unless there's something I'm missing...$5 / 为什么人会喜欢吃辣的东西？从生物学的角度来看，这是违反直觉的。#$e#难道有什么我没想到的……$5",
        "Shop_Abigail": "Hey, I grabbed some random stuff out of my closet. Want any of it? / 哎，我从衣柜里随便拿了些东西，有没有你想要的？",
        "GrandpaMasteryNote": "My dear {0}, / 亲爱的{0}：^^If you're reading this note, you've found the secret room I've prepared for you.^^Within these walls are tips, recipes, and even some of my most cherished tools... all the very best from the many happy years I spent in the valley.^^By coming this far, you'll have proven that you possess the skill and wisdom to make good use of these powerful secrets.^^I hope my discoveries help you in your journey to making {1} Farm a shining star of the whole world!^^Make me proud!^-Grandpa / ^既然你在看这张纸条了，说明你已经找到了我给你准备的秘密房间。^^这里有提示、配方，甚至还有我珍藏的一些工具……我在星露谷度过了快乐的岁月，攒下的家什都在这里了。^^你走到了这一步，证明你技术过硬、足智多谋，可以好好利用这些强大的秘宝。^^希望我的这些发现能够助你一臂之力，让{1}农场能够闪耀全世界！^^继续努力吧！^——爷爷",
        "Scholar_Question_0_2": "Question 1: Where are we? / 问题 1：我们现在在什么地方？",
        "Cook_DishNames_4_1": "Rainforest Shrimp / 雨林虾仁",
        "MagicHairDye_Name": "Magic Hair Gel / 魔法发胶",
        "Cook_DishNames_2_4": "Rumpled Fruit Skin / 皱果皮",
        "MakeOver_Emily_Reaction5": "Here, catch! / 喂，接着！",
        "Shop_Clint": "Need any ores? / 需要矿石吗？",
        "DF_Mine_CalicoStatue_Description_10": "Speed Boost / 加速",
        "DF_Mine_Explanation_2": "Your \"Egg Rating\" determines the likelihood of finding Calico Eggs. / 找到卡利科三花蛋的概率取决于你的“三花蛋分数”。^^\"Egg Rating\" increases every 5 levels down, as well as whenever you activate a Calico Statue.^ / ^每下降 5 层或者激活一座卡利科三花雕像，你就会获得“三花蛋分数”。^",
        "ParrotEgg_Chance_2": "high / 较高",
        "Cook_DishNames_0_4": "Spicy Tacos / 辣味墨西哥卷饼",
        "Gil_Rating_5to9": "...{0}? That's not too impressive, but at least you had the gumption to try. Here's a little something. / ……{0} 分？也就一般般吧，但你至少有魄力去尝试。给你一点小奖励。",
        "Race_Close": "That's the last race for today. We'll see you tomorrow! / 今天的比赛到此结束。我们明天见！",
        "GoldClock_On": "Turn the Golden Clock back on? / 要启动黄金时钟吗？",
        "DeluxeCheesePress_Name": "Deluxe Cheese Press / 高级压酪机",
        "Shop_Haley": "You'd better go find more eggs so you can buy all my stuff! / 你要不要再多弄一些三花蛋？那样就可以把我的东西全买走了！",
        "BasiliskPaw_Description": "You are immune to debuffs. / 免疫负面效果。",
        "TravelingMerchant_DF_Closed": "Closed until noon. / 正午开门。",
        "IridiumSpur_Name": "Golden Spur / 黄金马刺",
        "CactusMan_No": "Cactus Man: I understand. They may be small, but accepting a cactus into your life is big responsibility. Come back when you're feeling ready. / 仙人掌商人：我明白。仙人掌虽然很小，但迎接它的到来就要承担很多责任。等你准备好再回来吧。",
        "SkillName_1": "Fishing / 钓鱼",
        "Cook_Ingredient1": "Cave Loaf / 洞穴面包",
        "Race_Begin": "The next race is about to begin... / 下一场比赛即将开始……",
        "Instant": "Instant / 瞬间",
        "DesertFestival_Clint": "Hey, @. To tell you the truth, I don't really like festivals.#$b#But I'd feel even worse if I stayed at home, knowing that everyone else was out here having fun.$s / 哎，@，说句实话，我不太喜欢节日。#$b#但假如我待在家里，想到其他人都在外面玩得很开心，我会感觉更糟。$s",
        "FishFrenzy_forest": "{1} {0} frenzy has begun in Cindersap Forest. / 煤矿森林中掀起了{0}狂潮。",
        "DesertFestival_Jas": "This is fun, but I wish I had an ice cream... / 我很开心，但要是能吃冰淇淋就更好了……",
        "GoldenParrot_Tonight": "*Awk*... Sleep! *Awk*... We do it tonight! / （叽叽喳喳）……睡觉！（叽叽喳喳）……今晚开始！",
        "ButterflyPowder_Question": "Are you sure? {0} will be permanently removed from your farm. / 你确定吗？{0}被驱逐出农场之后就永远不会回来了。",
        "DesertFestival_Robin": "Hey @. We're just chewing the fat over here. I don't see these guys very often, even though we're neighbors! / 哎，@，我们就是随便聊聊。这帮人虽然是我邻居，但是平时不常见到！",
        "BlessingOfWaters": "Blessing Of Waters / 水域祝福",
        "LearnedANewPower": "You've learned a new power! / 你学会了新的能力！",
        "Cook_DishNames_0_1": "Earthy Mousse / 泥土慕斯",
        "PastaPrimavera_Name": "Pasta Primavera / 蔬菜意面",
        "Race_Comment_1": "That was a close one! / 太惊险了！",
        "Shady_Guy_Intro_2": "Suspicious Guy: ... Say, I got a little 'proposition' for ya. / 可疑的家伙：……是这样，我这有一个小小的“提案”。",
        "Shop_Demetrius": "Do you have any eggs to trade? I'm studying the composition of the shell. / 你手里有三花蛋可以交换吗？我在研究蛋壳的成分。",
        "CursedMannequinDemale_Name": "Cursed Mannequin (F) / 被诅咒的假人模特（女）",
        "MakeOver_Emily_Reaction1": "Oops, sorry if that tickles. / 哎呀，可能有点痒，不好意思。",
        "Marlon_Intro": "Hey there, @. Welcome to the Adventurer's Guild Challenge Booth.#$b#Every day, we'll have a pair of challenges for you to choose from. Complete one, and the guild will reward you with a bounty of Calico Eggs.#$b#Once you've selected a challenge, you won't be able to change your decision, so choose carefully! / 你好啊，@。欢迎来到探险家公会挑战摊位。#$b#每天，我们会提供两个挑战供你选择。选择一个完成后，公会就会奖励你大量卡利科三花蛋。#$b#一旦你选定了挑战就无法再更改，一定要谨慎选择！",
        "frog_variant_0": "Green Frog Egg / 绿蛙蛋",
        "trade_books": "Trade In Books / 回收书籍",
        "Spouse_Goodnight1": "Coming to bed? / 要睡觉了吗？",
        "Cook_Ingredient0": "Hearty Beans / 丰盛的豆子",
        "DesertFestival_Lewis3": "Remember, today is the last day of the festival. We'll be back next year, though. / 别忘了，今天是节日的最后一天。不过我们明年还会回来的。",
        "IceRod_Name": "Ice Rod / 寒冰法杖",
        "SquidFestBooth_NoRewards": "You haven't earned any rewards yet. Better start catching some squid! / 你还没有赢得奖品，赶紧开始钓鱿鱼吧！",
        "Shop_Marnie": "I found an extra roll of wallpaper from my house. It's yours for 20 eggs! / 我家里多了一卷墙纸，20 个三花蛋卖给你！",
        "HeavyFurnace_coal": "Requires 3 Coal / 需要 3 块煤炭。",
        "AttackEnchantment": "+{0} Attack / +{0} 攻击",
        "SquidFest_AlreadyGotAvailableRewards": "You don't have any rewards available right now. Keep catching more squid! / 目前没有可以获取的奖励了，继续钓更多鱿鱼吧！",
        "Cook_Sauce3": "Pungent Garlic / 刺鼻蒜蓉",
        "MakeOver_Emily_3": "Okay, I've got it!$h#$b#I'm coming in, so don't be alarmed! / 好了，我想好了！$h#$b#别慌啊，我进来了！",
        "DesertFestival_Sebastian": "Hey. I'm just hanging out with this bird. She seems to like me. / 你好，我在逗这只鸟，她好像很喜欢我。",
        "ButterflyPowder_Goodbye": "Goodbye, {0}... / 再见了，{0}……",
        "Race_Late_Guess": "Race Announcer: Whoops. Looks like the race has already started. Try again later! / 比赛播报员：比赛好像已经开始了，稍后再来试试吧！",
        "Race_Lose": "Better luck next time! / 下次好运！",
        "DF_Mine_CalicoStatue_Name_4": "Assassin Bugs / 刺客臭虫",
        "ParrotEgg_Chance_3": "very high / 极高",
        "Raccoon_interim_3": "Raccoon: Now we can grow the family bigger... / 浣熊：我们可以迎接新的家庭成员了……",
        "DF_Mine_CalicoStatue_Name_16": "10 Egg Treasure / 10 个蛋礼包",
        "Scholar_Question_0_1": "Question 1: What is the date of the season's end? / 问题 1：季节的最后一天是几号？",
        "Race_Ready": "On your marks... / 各就各位……",
        "DF_Mine_CalicoStatue_Name_13": "No Effect / 无效果",
        "GameMenu_Powers": "Special Items & Powers / 特殊物品与能力",
        "Cook_DishNames_1_0": "Mountain Chili / 农家辣汤",
        "Marlon_Challenge_Chosen": "Still working on the challenge, huh?#$b#Well, here it is, in case you needed a reminder. / 还在努力完成挑战是吧？#$b#嗯，给你提个醒，挑战内容是这个。",
        "IceRod_Description": "Shoots an orb of ice every {0} seconds, freezing any enemies in its path for {1} seconds. / 每隔 {0} 秒发射一个冰球，将路径上的所有敌人冻结 {1} 秒。",
        "Mayo_reaction3": "Umm... / 唔……",
        "GetRewards": "Get Rewards / 获取奖励",
        "ForestPylonEvent": "communityCenter/-2000 -2000/farmer 16 5 0 Wizard -1000 -1000 2/pause 1000/viewport 16 5 true/move farmer -2 0 1/pause 4000/playSound terraria_warp/specificTemporarySprite terraria_warp_begin/faceDirection farmer 2 true/animate farmer false true 100 94/jump farmer/pause 2000/stopAnimation farmer/faceDirection farmer 1/pause 3600/playSound coin/pause 100/awardFestivalPrize meowmere/pause 1000/specificTemporarySprite terraria_cat_leave/pause 5000/emote farmer 8/pause 500/warp Wizard 4 4/playSound doorClose/pause 400/faceDirection Wizard 1/emote Wizard 12/speak Wizard \"Don't touch that!\"/faceDirection farmer 3/emote farmer 16 true/end / communityCenter/-2000 -2000/farmer 16 5 0 Wizard -1000 -1000 2/pause 1000/viewport 16 5 true/move farmer -2 0 1/pause 4000/playSound terraria_warp/specificTemporarySprite terraria_warp_begin/faceDirection farmer 2 true/animate farmer false true 100 94/jump farmer/pause 2000/stopAnimation farmer/faceDirection farmer 1/pause 3600/playSound coin/pause 100/awardFestivalPrize meowmere/pause 1000/specificTemporarySprite terraria_cat_leave/pause 5000/emote farmer 8/pause 500/warp Wizard 4 4/playSound doorClose/pause 400/faceDirection Wizard 1/emote Wizard 12/speak Wizard \"不要碰啊！\"/faceDirection farmer 3/emote farmer 16 true/end",
        "Cook_DishNames_3_1": "Stuffed Mushrooms / 填馅蘑菇",
        "Shop_Penny": "Hi! I hope you find something you like. / 嗨！希望这里有你喜欢的东西。",
        "Racer_1": "King Sting / 毒刺蝎王",
        "DesertFestival_Marnie": "Hey, @. I was just thinking about milk.#$e#Would you ever try camel's milk? I've heard it's salty. / 哎，@，我在想动物奶的事情。#$e#你喝过骆驼奶吗？据说味道是咸的。",
        "frog_variant_1": "Brown Frog Egg / 棕蛙蛋",
        "options_menubg_0": "Standard / 标准",
        "Willy_DesertFishing3": "Willy: A fish swallowed me rare golden bobber! There's 30 eggs for whoever returns it. / 威利：有条鱼吞了我宝贝的黄金浮漂！谁能找到就给他 30 个蛋。",
        "CactusMan_Yes_4": "Cactus Man: I won't say why... but this one is the perfect match for you. / 仙人掌商人：这一株最适合你……理由不便透露。",
        "CactusMan_Yes_Intro": "Cactus Man: Great. Let's see... / 仙人掌商人：很好。我来看看……",
        "SquidFest_Pam": "I don't have the chops to catch squid, but that's fine. I'll just cheer you on from here, kid. / 我没有钓鱿鱼的本事，不过没关系，我会在这里为你加油的。",
        "DesertFestival_Lewis": "After a long, dark winter, this festival is a good way to revive everyone. / 度过漫长、黑暗的冬天之后，举办这么个节日能让大家重振精神。",
        "Decline": "Decline / 拒绝",
        "DF_Mine_CalicoStatue_Description_17": "100 Calico Eggs! / 100 个卡利科三花蛋！",
        "MonsterQuestTitle": "Bounty: {0} / 赏金：{0}",
        "Scholar_Question_0_0": "Question 1: Who runs the {0} in Pelican Town? / 问题 1：鹈鹕镇的{0}是谁在经营？",
        "MakeOver_Sandy_AlreadyStyled": "Not half bad, sweetie!$h#$b#Come back soon, I'll have a new look waiting for you! / 不错嘛，小可爱！$h#$b#以后多来找我，给你准备新的穿搭！",
        "DesertFestival_Haley2": "%Haley is glistening in the sunlight. / %海莉在阳光下闪闪发光。",
        "Cook_ChoseSauce": "Chef: Very good. A healthy drizzle of {0} to round out the dish. / 厨师：非常好，浇上健康的{0}，让菜肴更加美味。",
        "DwarfStatue_3": "Bombs cannot damage you. / 炸弹无法对你造成伤害。",
        "Race_Question": "Race Announcer: Guess the winner and receive some fabulous prizes! / 比赛播报员：猜猜谁会获胜，猜对即可获得大奖！",
        "DesertFestival_Elliott": "*mumble* ...hmm, the toe-feel is milky, but with plenty of body. Still, a bit mellower than back home...#$b#Oh, pardon me! I've become something of a sand connoisseur.$h / （喃喃自语）……唔，用脚趾感觉像牛奶，但比较粘稠，不过还是比家那边的更丝滑……#$b#啊，不好意思！我快要变成沙子鉴赏家了。$h",
        "FishingDerbySign": "[textcolor black][letterbg LooseSprites\\\\troutDerbyLetterBG 0]        -----Trout Derby----- / [textcolor black][letterbg LooseSprites\\\\troutDerbyLetterBG 0]        ——— 鳟鱼大赛 ———^^This weekend, Summer 20th through 21st:^^Come prove your freshwater skills and win prizes!^^(Note: Any personal items found near this sign will be sent to the lost and found) / ^本周末，夏季 20 日至 21 日：^^快来展示淡水钓鱼技术，赢取丰厚奖品！^^（注意：在此标志附近发现的个人物品将送至失物招领处）",
        "greenrainmessage": "A green rain has descended upon the valley. / 星露谷下起了绿色的雨。",
        "SlimeSlayerEnchantment": "Slime Slayer / 史莱姆专杀",
        "Scholar_Question_2_0_Options": "Carp,Pufferfish,Salmon,Squid / 鲤鱼,河豚,鲑鱼,鱿鱼",
        "Renovation_AddDiningRoom": "Add Dining Room/Adds a large room to the left of the kitchen./Select an area for the renovation. / 修建餐厅/在厨房左边增加一个大房间。/选择装修区域。",
        "DesertFestival_Sam_marriage": "Hey, don't forget to pick up our free cactus before the festival ends.#$b#Whatever it looks like, it's gonna be perfect in our house!$h / 哎，别忘了在节日结束前去领我们的免费仙人掌。#$b#不管它长什么样，放在我们家肯定很合适！$h",
        "DriedFlowers_name": "Dried {0} / {0}的干花",
        "DesertFestival_Emily3_marriage": "I can't remember... did I feed the parrot this morning? / 今天早上我喂鹦鹉了吗？记不清了……",
        "Marnie_Counter": "'I'm not around, but you can still make a purchase using the animal catalogue!'  -Marnie / “我现在不在，你可以用动物目录来买东西！”——玛妮",
        "Pam_busSign_generic": "I'm off duty today, kid! You'll have to drive yourself.       -Pam / 年轻人，我今天休息！你自己开车吧。——潘姆",
        "DesertFestival_Sam": "Hey, @. Check out my cactus. I'm trying to think of a name for him.#$e#Hmm... maybe '%name'? / 哎，@，来看看我的仙人掌。我在想给它起什么名字比较好。#$e#唔……要么就叫“%name”？",
        "Scholar_Question_0_1_Answers": "28th,30th,31st,26th / 28 日,30 日,31 日,26 日",
        "Willy_DesertFishing2": "Willy's Challenge: Catch a Scorpion Carp. / 威利的挑战：钓一条蝎鲤鱼。",
        "frog_variant_7": "Prismatic Frog Egg / 五彩蛙蛋",
        "Racer_2": "Shoebiscuit / 靴靴饼干",
        "Race_Set": "Get set... / 预备……",
        "Mastery": "Mastery: / 精通：",
        "MakeOver_Emily_1": "Okay, before we continue, let me visualize your aura, to see what kind of style will make you happiest... / 好了，在开始之前，我要想象一下你的气质，看看哪种风格跟你最搭……",
        "Marlon_2": "Feeling the adventurer's spirit?#$b#Good, here are today's challenges. / 忍不住想要去探险了吗？#$b#很好，今天的挑战在这里。",
        "FishingDerby_Exclamation1": "A bite! / 咬钩了！",
        "skillBook_Category": "Skill Book / 技能书",
        "WizardCatalogueDescription": "M. Rasmodius' private furniture collection. / M·拉斯莫迪斯的私人家具收藏。",
        "MakeOver_Emily_Reaction2": "Yikes, sorry if that hurt! / 哎哟，如果弄痛你了实在抱歉！",
        "DF_Mine_CalicoStatue_Name_17": "100 Egg Treasure / 100 个蛋礼包",
        "Freezer_description": "Items placed inside will lose their quality overnight. / 放在里面的东西过夜后品质会降低。",
        "Fizz_Sweet": "Hee Hee! / 嘻嘻嘻！",
        "Shop_Maru": "See anything you like? / 有你喜欢的东西吗？",
        "books_buy_welcome": "Marcello's Books... At your service! / 我是马尔赛罗，这里的书……请随意挑选！",
        "Race_Guess_Already_Made": "Race Announcer: Let's see if {0} can pull this off! / 比赛播报员：{0}能否获胜，让我们拭目以待！",
        "Shady_Guy_NoEgg": "Suspicious Guy: Looks like you don't have any Calico Eggs, kid. Stop wastin' my time. / 可疑的家伙：${小子^小姑娘}$，你好像压根没有卡利科三花蛋。别浪费我时间。",
        "Willy_Challenge": "Willy's Challenge / 威利的挑战",
        "FishFrenzy_mountain": "{1} {0} frenzy has begun in the mountains. / 山里掀起了{0}狂潮。",
        "SpiritsEveCart": "Take the secret shortcut back? / 走秘密捷径回去吗？",
        "PerfectMagicQuiver": "Perfect Magic Quiver / 完美魔法箭筒",
        "Gil_Rating_50": "{0}!?!?!?!?!?!?!?$h / {0} 分？！！！！！！！$h",
        "CursedMannequinMale_Name": "Cursed Mannequin (M) / 被诅咒的假人模特（男）",
        "Mayo_reaction0": "Gross! / 好恶心！",
        "DesertFestival_Alex": "Have you seen the size of these Calico Eggs?#$b#Just imagine the protein... / 这些卡利科三花蛋也太大了吧！#$b#满满的蛋白质……",
        "Shop_Vincent": "Hi! Um... I found some stuff. Wanna buy it!? / 嗨！呃……我翻出来了一些东西，想买吗？！",
        "PetBowlName": "{0}'s Bowl / {0}的碗",
        "DesertFestival_Sebastian_marriage": "Hey, I'll just stay here and relax in the shade.#$e#You know how I am... I've always been more of a cave dweller.$h / 哎，我就待在这儿，在阴凉处歇一会儿。#$e#你懂的……我一直是比较宅的人。$h",
        "FishingDerby_Exclamation0": "Got one! / 钓到了！",
        "TrashCatalogueDescription": "Access a free supply of trash decorations. Wash hands after use. / 可以免费获取垃圾装饰品，使用后记得洗手。",
        "DF_Mine_CalicoStatue_Name_14": "Tooth File / 牙齿锉刀",
        "Joja_Debt_Notice": "NOTICE: / 通知：^^At the end of the season, {0}g will be debited from your account.^^Failure to pay will result in a negative balance.^^Thank you for your patronage.^-JojaBank / ^季节结束时，将从您的账户划走 {0} 金。^^如果无力偿还，余额将变为负数。^^感谢您的惠顾。^——Joja 银行",
        "FishingDerby_Exclamation4": "C'mon now... / 就差一点……",
        "AdoptedPet": "Your new pet '{0}' has been sent to your home. / 你的新宠物“{0}”已经送到家中。",
        "MagicQuiver_Description": "Shoots a magic arrow at nearby enemies every {0} seconds, dealing {1}-{2} damage. / 每隔 {0} 秒向附近的敌人射出魔法箭，造成 {1}-{2} 点伤害。",
        "ChooseBobber": "Bobber Style: / 浮漂样式",
        "Race_Collect_Prize_Special": "Race Announcer: Escar-go... how?? Um...Well, here's your big payout... / 比赛播报员：闪电蜗牛……怎么可能？？呃……行吧，这是你的大奖……",
        "Raccoon_interim": "Raccoon: We're doing great, bobo... / 浣熊：波波，我们过得很好……",
        "DeluxeCrabPot_name": "Deluxe Crab Pot / 高级蟹笼",
        "BroccoliFusilli_Description": "A delightful pasta with broccoli and sun-dried tomatoes. / 放了西蓝花和番茄干的美味意大利面。",
        "Scholar_Question_2_0": "Question 3: In what season can you catch {0}? / 问题 3：你可以在哪个季节钓到{0}？",
        "SpringOnionMastery_Description": "Spring onions are worth 5x the gold. / 带叶洋葱的售价提高到了原先的 5 倍。",
        "Race_Win": "Come by to collect your prize! / 来领取你的奖励吧！",
        "CactusMan_Yes_2": "Cactus Man: This one's a little shy, but I know you'll become friends in no time. / 仙人掌商人：它有点害羞，但我相信你们很快就会成为朋友。",
        "HeavyFurnace_ores": "Requires 25 ores. / 需要 25 个矿石。",
        "Cook_Intro_Yes3": "Chef: Oohoo... *giggle*... very good. Now... what will you have? / 厨师：哦哦哦……呵呵……非常好。来吧……你想吃什么？",
        "Scholar_Question_1_1_Answers": "Spring,Summer,Fall / 春季,夏季,秋季",
        "Shop_Eggs": "T...Trade... E...Eggs... / 交……交换……三花……蛋……",
        "frog_variant_2": "Blue-Green Frog Egg / 蓝绿蛙蛋",
        "MannequinMale_Name": "Mannequin (M) / 假人模特（男）",
        "FishingDerby_Exclamation6": "Gotcha! / 好啊！",
        "Scholar_Question_2_1": "Question 3: How many steps have you taken? / 问题 3：你一共走了多少步？",
        "Marlon_3": "I hope you've kept your weapons maintained.#$b#You'll need them in top form for today's challenges. / 工欲善其事，必先利其器。#$b#武器锋利了才能完成今天的挑战。",
        "Fizz_Yes": "Yes (Costs 500,000g) / 是（花费 500,000 金）",
        "Willy_DesertFishing1": "\n        Willy's Challenge: Catch 3 Sandfish.\n       / 威利的挑战：钓 3 条沙鱼。",
        "FestivalTentWarning": "Tomorrow is a festival. / 明天会庆祝节日。",
        "Scholar_Question_1_2_Answers": "Wednesday,Thursday,Tuesday,Monday,Saturday,Sunday,Friday / 星期三,星期四,星期二,星期一,星期六,星期日,星期五",
        "DwarfStatue_2": "Greater chance to find coal. / 找到煤炭的几率更高。",
        "BlessingOfEnergy_description": "You have infinite energy. / 你的能量无限。",
        "Farm_Perfection_Description": "Waterfall Farm_Grandpa left you a magic lamp that grants a powerful bonus. However, you've also inherited his 1,000,000g debt to JojaBank, and must pay it off in seasonal installments... / 瀑布农场_爷爷留给你一盏神灯，可以获得强力加成，然而他在 Joja 银行的 1,000,000 金欠款也要由你按季节分期偿还……",
        "PowdermelonSoda_Description": "It naturally bubbles from the power of the melon skin. / 蕴含瓜皮的力量，会自然起泡。",
        "alreadyreadbook": "Reading this book again will grant some {0} experience. / 再次阅读这本书可以获得一些{0}经验。",
        "Marlon_Challenge_Finished": "Very good.#$b#There'll be more challenges tomorrow, so take it easy and get some rest. / 非常好。#$b#明天还会有更多挑战，现在可以放松休息一下了。",
        "DF_Mine_CalicoStatue_Description_15": "25 Calico Eggs / 25 个卡利科三花蛋",
        "Accept": "Accept / 接受",
        "DF_Mine_CalicoStatue_Name_11": "Full Refresh / 完全恢复",
        "Fizz_Intro_2": "So... what do you say? 500,000g for a bonafide 'Perfection Waiver'? / 好……怎么样？要花 500,000 金来一张货真价实的《完美豁免书》吗？",
        "DesertFestival_Penny": "Thousands of years ago, this place was the homeland of an ancient civilization. I wonder what they were like? / 几千年前，这片土地存在一个古代文明。不知道是什么样的呢？",
        "Race_Ongoing": "Race Announcer: The race is currently in progress! Let's talk later... / 比赛播报员：比赛正在进行中！等会儿再说……",
        "SquidFest_Willy": "After a while, you get a feel for the squid's behavior. You can tell when one's on the line before you even see it. / 钓多了你就会了解鱿鱼的习性，眼睛还没看到你就能感觉到有一只上钩了。",
        "MakeOver_Emily_2": "Yes... I see... / 哦……原来如此……",
        "Renovation_RemoveDiningRoom": "Remove Dining Room/Removes the large room to the left of the kitchen./Select an area for the renovation. / 拆除餐厅/拆除厨房左边的大房间。/选择装修区域。",
        "Farming_Mastery": "You can now find Golden Animal Crackers, which permanently doubles a farm animal's produce. Doesn't work on pigs. / 你可以找到金色动物饼干了，它可以使一只农场动物的产量永久翻倍，对猪无效。",
        "MakeOver_Sandy_3": "Knock, knock, honey! I'm coming in! / 小可爱！我要进来啦！",
        "Raccoon_intro_2": "Raccoon: Hungry... need mushroom... / 浣熊：饿了……想吃蘑菇……",
        "Cook_Intro_Yes2": "Chef: I'd like to make you a very special dish. Something perfectly suited to your unique taste. May I? / 厨师：我想为你做一道非常特别的、量身定制的菜，怎么样？",
        "DeluxeMayoMachine_Name": "Deluxe Mayonnaise Machine / 高级蛋黄酱机",
        "ResourceQuestTitle": "Gathering: {0} / 收集：{0}",
        "JojaFreeRun": "No Joja services used! / 没有使用 Joja 服务！",
        "alreadyreadbook_random": "Reading this book again will grant a small amount of experience in all areas. / 再次阅读这本书可以在所有领域获得少量经验。",
        "Racer_4": "Cactus Crawler / 爬爬仙人掌",
        "SkullCaveKickWarning": "Any players currently inside the Skull Cavern will be removed. Do you want to proceed? / 将会踢出现在位于骷髅洞穴里的所有玩家，要继续吗？",
        "MasteryCompleteToast": "You feel Grandpa's hand patting your shoulder... / 你感觉到爷爷拍了拍你的肩膀……",
        "options_menubg_1": "Graphical / 图形",
        "DesertFestival_Emily_marriage": "Hey, @! I love you just the way you are... but if you want, you can step inside the box too! / @！你现在这样挺好看的……不过你也可以考虑到箱子里来试试！",
        "Book_Category": "Book / 书",
        "Trinket": "Trinket / 饰品",
        "Raccoon_busy": "Another player is talking to the Raccoon right now. / 另一个玩家正在和浣熊交谈。",
        "Shop_Evelyn": "Hello dear. Please take your time, I'll be here all day! / 亲爱的，慢慢看吧，我今天一天都待在这里！",
        "DF_Mine_CalicoStatue_MP_Message": "Calico Statue: \"{0}\" has been activated. / 卡利科三花雕像：“{0}”已激活。",
        "DF_Mine_CalicoStatue_Description_5": "Lose more eggs when you're knocked out / 晕倒后掉落的三花蛋增多",
        "DF_Mine_CalicoStatue_Name_9": "Curse Of The Tomb / 墓碑诅咒",
        "DesertFestival_NowOpen": "The Desert Festival is now open! / 沙漠节现已开始！",
        "Raccoon_intro_1": "Raccoon: Hungry... need fruit... / 浣熊：饿了……想吃水果……",
        "DeluxeLoom_Description": "This can process 3 pieces of wool at a time. / 可以同时加工 3 团动物毛。",
        "Scholar_Win": "Scholar: Very Good! I'm impressed with your knowledge, friend. Here is your prize. / 学者：非常好！朋友，你知识渊博，我很佩服。给你奖品。",
        "Mayo_reaction2": "Why?! / 你怎么？！",
        "4_Mastery": "Combat Mastery / 战斗精通",
        "FishingDerby_Exclamation3": "Felt a nibble! / 好像咬钩了！",
        "Race_Ended": "Race Announcer: The races have ended for the day. I hope you had fun! / 比赛播报员：今天的比赛已经结束了，希望你看得开心！",
        "BooksellerInTown": "The Bookseller is in town today. / 书摊老板今天在镇上。",
        "Raccoon_interim_2": "Raccoon: Now, we start a family... / 浣熊：我们可以组建家庭了……",
        "GoldenParrot": "*Awk*... Money! *Awk*... Find golden walnuts! / （叽叽喳喳）……钱！（叽叽喳喳）……找到金核桃！",
        "2_Mastery": "Foraging Mastery / 采集精通",
        "MakeOver_Sandy_Done": "You're looking radiant!#$b#I've put your old clothes in your backpack in case you have a change of heart.$h / 你现在简直是光彩照人！#$b#假如你穿厌了可以换回旧衣服，我放在你背包里了。$h",
        "EggShop_Closed": "The shop isn't open. Come back later. / 商店没开门，请稍后再来。",
        "Fishing_Mastery": "You can now encounter Golden Fishing Chests. / 你可以遇到金色钓鱼宝箱了。",
        "Renovation_CloseDiningRoom": "Close Dining Room/Restores the wall between the dining room and kitchen./Select an area for the renovation. / 隔开餐厅/恢复餐厅和厨房之间的隔墙。/选择装修区域。",
        "Shop_Caroline": "Hello. I hope you see something you like. / 你好啊，看看有没有你喜欢的东西。",
        "FishingDerby_Exclamation5": "Got a bite! / 上钩了！",
        "FrogEgg_Name": "Frog Egg / 青蛙蛋",
        "DesertFestival_Pam": "Hey, kid... You takin' the day off? It's nice to kick back every once in a while, isn't it?#$e#Yep... Even ol' Pam needs some sunlight on her skin now and then! Just wake me up before I turn into leather... Heheh. / 哎，孩子……你今天休息吗？偶尔放松一下也挺好的，是不是？#$e#对啊……即使是我这把老骨头偶尔也要晒晒太阳！在我晒干之前叫醒我就行……呵呵……",
        "Race_Guess": "Race Announcer: Who do you think will win? / 比赛播报员：你觉得谁会获胜？",
        "AdoptPets": "Adopt Pets / 领养宠物",
        "Willy_Challenge_Return_3": "Well, if it isn't me favorite golden bobber!#$b#And it only smells mild o' fish... Heh heh.$h#$b#Here's 30 Calico Eggs for your reward. / 嗯，这不是我最喜欢的黄金浮漂吗！#$b#就是有股鱼腥味……嘿嘿。$h#$b#给你奖励，30 个卡利科三花蛋。",
        "TownTreeWarning": "I shouldn't cut down trees in town. / 我不应该在镇上砍树。",
        "Cook_Intro": "Chef: Why hello, there... hungry? / 厨师：你好啊……你饿不饿？",
        "Scholar_Closed": "Scholar: Forgive me, friend. But I cannot engage with you until the festival is open. / 学者：朋友，实在抱歉，等节日开始之后我才能和你交流。",
        "DF_Mine_CalicoStatue_Name_12": "50 Egg Treasure / 50 个蛋礼包",
        "ForestMagic_Description": "You are one with forest magic... / 你拥有森林的魔法……",
        "Gil_Rating_20to24": "{0}? Okay, now I'm impressed...#$b#Hey, Marlon! Get a load of this... an Egg Rating of {0} for the day! / {0} 分？哦，那确实很厉害啊……#$b#喂，马龙！快来看看……今天最高的有 {0} 分！",
        "DF_Mine_CalicoStatue_Name_2": "Skeleton Invasion / 骷髅来袭",
        "Raccoon_interim_1": "Raccoon: Now, maybe I find a wife... / 浣熊：好了，我或许能找到老婆……",
        "Scholar_DoneThisYear": "Scholar: Enjoy the eggs, my friend. I'll be back next year for another challenge. / 学者：朋友，希望这些三花蛋对你有用。明年我会再来给你出难题。",
        "lumberjack_profession_possible": "Removing a wild tree stump always produces a seed. / 砍掉野树树桩总会掉落一个种子。",
        "Shady_Guy_Selected_2": "Suspicious Guy: {0} it is. Now excuse me, I've got a phone call to make... / 可疑的家伙：你选{0}是吧。等我打个电话……",
        "Gil_Rating_25": "{0}!?!#$b#Well, I'll be... We've got a real Calico Egg hunter here!  / {0} 分？！！#$b#真的假的……你这收割三花蛋的水平真是一绝！",
        "Willy_Challenge_Return_1": "Ah, you got 'em. An exciting catch, aren't they?#$b#Here's 25 Calico Eggs for your reward. / 啊，你钓到了。钓的时候是不是很刺激？#$b#给你奖励，25 个卡利科三花蛋。",
        "DesertFestival_Emily": "Hmm... I'm sensing that your fashion doesn't quite match your inner feeling. Just step in the box and we'll fix you up! / 唔……我能感受到，你的穿搭不太符合你的内心。走到这个箱子里面，我们让你焕然一新！",
        "Gil_Rating_15to19": "{0}... that ain't bad at all. That's the kind of number we're looking for in the Adventurer's Guild. Here's your prize. / {0} 分……相当不错啊，探险家公会就是想要这种水平的。给你奖励。",
        "Raccoon_intro_3": "Raccoon: Thirsty... need juice... / 浣熊：渴了……想喝蔬菜汁……",
        "CactusMan_Yes_5": "Cactus Man: This one's got a strange look, but it suits you. / 仙人掌商人：这一株看起来有点奇怪，但很适合你。",
        "FishingDerbyBooth_Intro": "Welcome to the Trout Derby! What can I do for you? / 欢迎来到鳟鱼大赛！您有什么事？",
        "Waiver_Note": "You got a 'perfection waiver'! (Total: {0}.) / 你获得了一张《完美豁免书》！（总数：{0} 张。）",
        "Willy_Challenge_Return_2": "Ah, you did it. A challenging catch, don't you think?#$b#Here's 50 Calico Eggs for your reward. / 啊，你成功了。还挺难钓的吧，你觉得呢？#$b#给你奖励，50 个卡利科三花蛋。",
        "books_welcome": "Welcome to Marcello's Books! / 我是马尔赛罗，欢迎来到我的书摊！",
        "Mayo_reaction4": "Yummie! / 不错哦！",
        "DF_Mine_CalicoStatue_Description_13": "No effect / 无效果",
        "Scholar_Question_3_2": "Question 4: How many garbage cans are there in Pelican Town? / 问题 4：鹈鹕镇有多少个垃圾桶？",
        "DeluxeCrabPot_description": "This will catch more than a regular crab pot. / 能比普通蟹笼捕到更多东西。",
        "DwarfStatue_0": "+1 ore from ore nodes. / 每个采矿点 +1 个矿石。"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Strings/animationDescriptions",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "sam_guitar": "%Sam is busy practicing the guitar. / %山姆正忙着弹吉他。",
        "sam_pool": "$c .5#Hmm... If I give the cue ball a bit of a top spin, maybe I could...$7#$e#*Sigh*... I'm not very good.$s / $c .5#唔……如果我用高杆打母球，说不定我能……$7#$e#*唉*……我做得不好。$s",
        "abigail_videogames": "Urghh... I died again! This game is so hard...$u / 啊啊……我还是不能打通“草原之王的冒险之旅”的第一关！$u",
        "marnie_exercise": "%Marnie smiles at you through a mist of sweat. / %玛妮透过一层薄汗朝你微笑。",
        "harvey_examine_left": "Now just hold still... Take a deep breath for me.$u / 待着别动……我要你深吸一口气。$u",
        "caroline_exercise": "Don't look! I'm all red and sweaty.$s / 别盯着我！我全身红扑扑的，到处都是汗。$s",
        "penny_wave_left": "This town's safe, but I always walk the children home anyway. / 这个镇子很安全，但我还是一直陪孩子们回家。",
        "haley_photo": "%Haley's too involved with her camera to notice you. / %海莉的注意力全在相机上，没有注意到你。",
        "demetrius_dance": "%Demetrius is busy. / %德米特里厄斯在忙。",
        "sam_skateboarding": "%Sam's trying to do a kickflip. / %山姆正尝试回旋踢。",
        "emily_exercise": "Exercising can be fun! / 锻炼很有趣的！",
        "sam_work": "%Sam's on the clock... better not get him in trouble. / %山姆正在上班……最好不要给他添麻烦。",
        "harvey_radio": "%Harvey looks busy right now. / %哈维现在看起来很忙。",
        "shane_work": "%Shane's hard at work. He doesn't seem interested in talking. / %谢恩正在努力工作。似乎没兴趣聊天。",
        "robin_dance": "%Robin is busy. / %罗宾在忙。",
        "jodi_exercise": "Ungh... Breathe in.... Ungh.... Breathe out.$4 / 呃……吸气……呃……呼气。$4",
        "robin_exercise": "My arms are strong... *pant*... but my legs need work... *gasp* / 我的手臂很强壮……*喘气*……但是我的腿还需要再锻炼……* 喘气 *",
        "vincent_read_right": "Ms. Penny says I have to read this book before I can go play.$s / 潘妮小姐说我在去玩之前必须先读一读这本书。$s",
        "demetrius_read": "We're insulated from the rest of the world here in Stardew Valley. Maybe that's a good thing. / 我们星露谷这里可算是与世隔绝。说不定这是一件好事。",
        "sam_gameboy": "One sec... I gotta beat this level.$7 / 等下……我能过这关。$7",
        "alex_lift_weights": "Unghh... Can't talk.$6 / 啊……没法说话。$6"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Strings/BigCraftables",
