      "Entries": {
        "RareCrow_1_Description": "Collect them all! (1 of 8) / 将它们全部收齐！（8-1）",
        "AncientTable_Description": "It's covered in the thickest cobwebs. / 满满都是蛛网的桌子。",
        "RitualMask_Name": "Ritual Mask / 仪式面具",
        "Tapper_Name": "Tapper / 树液采集器",
        "SlimeBall_Description": "Filled with slime. / 满是粘液的物体。",
        "SeasonalPlant_Name": "Seasonal Plant / 季节性植物",
        "Door_Name": "Door / 门",
        "TablePieceL_Description": "The left side of a big table. / 一张大桌子的左角。",
        "WoodLamppost_Name": "Wood Lamp-post / 木灯柱",
        "OstrichIncubator_Description": "Hatches ostrich eggs into baby ostriches. Place in a barn. / 将鸵鸟蛋孵化成鸵鸟雏鸟。放置在畜棚里。",
        "SeedMaker_Description": "Place crops inside to produce a varying amount of seeds. Doesn't work with fruit tree crops. / 将作物放入，将会产出各种各样的种子。对果树类的作物无效。",
        "SkullBrazier_Name": "Skull Brazier / 骷髅火炬",
