        "DeluxeScarecrow_Name": "Deluxe Scarecrow / 豪华稻草人",
        "LockedDoor_Name": "Locked Door / 上锁的门",
        "JunimoChest_Description": "Through the power of forest magic, every Junimo Chest links to the same stash. / 通过森林魔法的力量，每个祝尼魔箱都连接到同一个储存处。",
        "SlothSkeletonL_Name": "Sloth Skeleton L / 树懒骨架（左）",
        "BasicLog_Name": "Basic Log / 普通圆木",
        "Bonfire_Description": "The red embers glow softly. / 余烬徐徐燃烧。",
        "HeavyFurnace_Name": "Heavy Furnace / 重型熔炉",
        "RareCrow_1_Name": "Rarecrow / 珍奇乌鸦",
        "SignOfTheVessel_Name": "Sign Of The Vessel / 船标",
        "RareCrow_3_Description": "Collect them all! (3 of 8) / 将它们全部收齐！（8-3）",
        "Cask_Description": "Use in the cellar to age products like wine and cheese. / 在地窖中使用以使产品变陈，如葡萄酒和奶酪。",
        "BeeHouse_Name": "Bee House / 蜂房",
        "Boulder_Description": "An extremely dense piece of stone. / 一块非常沉重的石头。",
        "AutoPetter_Description": "Joja Co. patented technology for coops and barns. Keeps your animals content, but can't replace the full benefit of human touch. Hand-petting can be provided to supplement. / Joja 公司专利技术，适用于鸡舍和畜棚。可以让动物们满足，但是无法实现亲自抚摸的所有好处。使用后仍可手动抚摸来补足。",
        "RareCrow_4_Description": "Collect them all! (4 of 8) / 将它们全部收齐！（8-4）",
        "HeavyTapper_Description": "Place on a maple, oak, or pine tree and wait for the reservoir to fill with product! Works twice as fast as a normal tapper. / 放在枫树、橡树、松树上，然后等着装满树液吧！比普通树液采集器快一倍。",
        "JunimoChest_Name": "Junimo Chest / 祝尼魔箱",
        "CoffeeMaker_Description": "Automatically brews a fresh cup every morning. / 每天早上自动煮一杯新鲜的咖啡。",
        "DeadTree_Name": "Dead Tree / 枯死的树",
        "SlimeEggPress_Name": "Slime Egg-Press / 史莱姆压蛋器",
        "Hopper_Name": "Hopper / 加料器",
        "MushroomBox_Description": "Mushrooms grow every few days / 每过几天就会长出蘑菇。",
        "SingingStone_Description": "It rings out with a pure tone when struck. / 被击中就会发出纯音。",
        "Bongo_Name": "Bongo / 小手鼓",
        "PlushBunny_Name": "Plush Bunny / 绒毛兔子",
        "AutoGrabber_Description": "Automatically harvests from your animals each morning. Must be placed inside a coop or barn. / 每天早晨自动采集动物产品。必须放在鸡舍或畜棚内。",
        "MarbleBrazier_Description": "Provides a moderate amount of light. / 提供一点亮光。",
        "RareCrow_7_Description": "Collect them all! (7 of 8) / 将它们全部收齐！（8-7）",
        "Crate_Name": "Crate / 木箱",
        "StatueOfPerfection_Description": "It's made of pure iridium. / 由纯铱打造而成。",
        "WickedStatue_LitEyes_Name": "Wicked Statue / 邪恶雕像",
        "RareCrow_3_Name": "Rarecrow / 珍奇乌鸦",
        "Heater_Name": "Heater / 加热器",
        "CheesePress_Name": "Cheese Press / 压酪机",
        "BoneMill_Description": "Turns bone items into fertilizers. / 可以把骨头制成肥料。",
        "GardenPot_Name": "Garden Pot / 花盆",
        "DriedSunflowers_Name": "Dried Sunflowers / 风干太阳花",
        "HMTGF_Name": "??HMTGF?? / ??HMTGF??",
        "MiniForge_Description": "Now, you can use a dwarvish forge from the convenience of your home. / 你可以在家中方便地使用矮人锻造台了。",
        "BoneMill_Name": "Bone Mill / 碎骨机",
        "GeodeCrusher_Description": "Breaks geodes open automatically. / 可以自动地破开晶球。",
        "Bonfire_Name": "Bonfire / 篝火",
        "SkeletonModel_Name": "Skeleton Model / 骨架模型",
        "MushroomBox_Name": "Mushroom Box / 蘑菇盒子",
        "TallTorch_Description": "The stem is made from bamboo. / 火把是用竹子打造的。",
        "Campfire_2_Description": "Cook on the go! / 随时随地做饭！",
        "LockedDoor_Description": "A hidden mechanism causes it to retract into the ground. / 一种使它缩回地面的隐蔽装置。",
        "Foroguemon_Description": "??Foroguemon?? / ??碎屑雕像??",
        "DeluxeWormBin_Description": "Produces Deluxe Bait on a regular basis. The worms are self-sufficient. / 定期产生高级鱼饵。里面的虫子可以自给自足。",
        "Keg_Description": "Place a fruit or vegetable in here. Eventually it will turn into a beverage. / 置放水果或蔬菜在内。最终会变成饮品。",
        "MarbleBrazier_Name": "Marble Brazier / 大理石火炬",
        "StardewHeroTrophy_Name": "Stardew Hero Trophy / 星露谷英雄奖杯",
        "StoneOwl_Secret_Name": "Stone Owl / 石猫头鹰",
        "Bookcase_Description": "A home for books. / 书本的家。",
        "FishSmoker_Description": "Place fish inside with a piece of coal to create smoked fish, which is worth double. The quality of the fish is preserved. / 放入鱼和一块煤炭即可烟熏，熏鱼价格是普通的两倍。",
        "DeluxeWormBin_Name": "Deluxe Worm Bin / 高级虫饵盒",
        "PinkyLemon_Name": "??Pinky Lemon?? / ??粉色柠檬??",
        "DecorativePitcher_Description": "Hand-made out of brass. / 用黄铜手工打造。",
        "FeedHopper_Description": "Provides convenient access to silo fodder. / 可以轻易进入饲料筒仓。",
        "CharcoalKiln_Name": "Charcoal Kiln / 煤炭窑",
