        "StoneParrot_Name": "Stone Parrot / 石鹦鹉",
        "StoneOwl_Decorative_Description": "Garden art for your farm. / 适合农场的园艺。",
        "Loom_Description": "Turns raw wool into fine cloth. / 将动物毛转换成美丽的布料。",
        "SingingStone_Name": "Singing Stone / 唱歌的石头",
        "Tapper_Description": "Place on a maple, oak, or pine tree and wait for the reservoir to fill with product! / 放在枫树、橡树、松树上，然后等着装满树液吧！",
        "Obelisk_Description": "A sinister-looking portal that radiates with evil energy. / 一个散发着邪恶能量的可怕传送阵。",
        "DarkSign_Description": "Use an item on this to change what's displayed. The item won't be consumed. / 在此上使用一个道具，即可改变显示的内容。道具不会被消耗掉。",
        "MiniObelisk_Description": "Place two on the farm to warp between them. / 在农场中放置两个，就可以在它们之间传送。",
        "SuitOfArmor_Name": "Suit Of Armor / 装甲",
        "EmptyCapsule_Description": "Part of the glass is shattered. / 一部分玻璃被击碎了。",
        "CarvedBrazier_Description": "Provides a moderate amount of light. / 提供一点亮光。",
        "PlushBunny_Description": "It's big, it's soft, and it's cute. / 很大、很软、很可爱。",
        "DarkSign_Name": "Dark Sign / 深色牌子",
        "Loom_Name": "Loom / 织布机",
        "ItemPedestal_Description": "A place to display an item. / A place to display an item.",
        "SuitOfArmor_Description": "A decorative piece for your farm. / 农场的装饰件。",
        "AncientTable_Name": "Ancient Table / 远古桌子",
        "Chest_Description": "A place to store your items. / 收藏你的物品的地方。",
        "WoodLamppost_Description": "Provides a good amount of light. / 提供不少亮光。",
        "StoneJunimo_Name": "Stone Junimo / 石祝尼魔",
        "MiniShippingBin_Description": "Items placed in it will be included in the nightly shipment. / 放在里面的物品会在每晚售出。",
        "IronLamppost_Description": "Provides a good amount of light. / 提供不少亮光。",
        "StoneCairn_Description": "A decorative piece for your farm. / 农场的装饰件。",
        "ObsidianVase_Name": "Obsidian Vase / 黑曜石花瓶",
        "Anvil_Name": "Anvil / 铁砧",
        "MayonnaiseMachine_Description": "Turns eggs into mayonnaise. / 将鸡蛋转换为蛋黄酱。",
        "PrairieKingArcadeSystem_Name": "Prairie King Arcade System / 草原之王街机系统",
        "GreenCanes_Description": "A decorative piece for your farm. / 农场的装饰件。",
        "SewingMachine_Description": "Use to tailor clothes from the convenience of your home! / 用来在家中方便地量身定做衣服！",
        "GraveStone_Description": "A decorative piece for your farm. / 农场的装饰件。",
        "GreenCanes_Name": "Green Canes / 绿杖",
        "DeluxeScarecrow_Description": "Prevents crows from attacking your crops. Has a large radius (about 16 \"tiles\"). / 阻止乌鸦攻击你的庄稼。范围很大（大约半径 16 格）。",
        "HeavyTapper_Name": "Heavy Tapper / 重型树液采集器",
        "SlothSkeletonM_Name": "Sloth Skeleton M / 树懒骨架（中）",
