        "ObsidianVase_Description": "A beautifully crafted ornamental vase made from obsidian and gold. / 一个由黑曜石和黄金打造的美丽装饰花瓶。",
        "HMTGF_Description": "??HMTGF?? / ??HMTGF??",
        "AutoGrabber_Name": "Auto-Grabber / 自动采集器",
        "Deconstructor_Description": "Destroys crafted items, but salvages their most valuable material. / 销毁打造的物品，回收最有价值的材料。",
        "Anvil_Description": "Allows you to re-forge trinkets, randomizing their stats. Costs 3 iridium bars per use. / 可以“重新锻造”饰品。每次使用消耗 3 块铱锭。",
        "ChickenStatue_Description": "A wooden statue of a chicken. / 一只母鸡的木质雕像。",
