        "LawnFlamingo_Description": "A decorative piece for your farm. / 农场的装饰件。",
        "HeavyFurnace_Description": "It's more efficient than a regular furnace. Requires 25 pieces of ore and 3 coal per use. / 比普通熔炉效率更高。每次使用需要 25 个矿石和 3 块煤炭。",
        "OilMaker_Name": "Oil Maker / 产油机",
        "WoodChair_Description": "A chair that can be oriented in 4 different ways. / 一种可面朝四个方向的椅子。",
        "MushroomLog_Name": "Mushroom Log / 蘑菇树桩",
        "Hopper_Description": "Items placed inside will automatically be loaded into the machine in front of it. / 把东西放进去，会自动加进前面的机器里。",
        "StoneBrazier_Description": "Provides a moderate amount of light. / 提供一点亮光。",
        "Scarecrow_Description": "Prevents crows from attacking your crops. Has a limited radius (about 8 \"tiles\"). / 防止乌鸦袭击你的农作物。范围有限（大约半径 8 格）。",
        "StoneOwl_Secret_Description": "It's not clear where this came from, but it looks very fine. / 不知道从哪儿来，但是挺耐看。",
        "DeadTree_Description": "It's been petrified for a long time, poor thing. / 已经风干了很久的可怜树木。",
        "RareCrow_4_Name": "Rarecrow / 珍奇乌鸦",
        "CharcoalKiln_Description": "Turns 10 pieces of wood into one piece of coal. / 将 10 块木头转换成一块煤炭。",
