        "StoneOwl_Decorative_Name": "Stone Owl / 石猫头鹰",
        "SlothSkeletonL_Description": "This extinct sloth roamed the lush, prehistoric forests of Stardew Valley. Its powerful jaw tore through the toughest plant fibers. / 这种已经灭绝的树懒曾经生活在星露谷的史前森林中。它强大的上下顎可以咬断最坚硬的植物纤维。",
        "ChickenStatue_Name": "Chicken Statue / 鸡雕像",
        "WormBin_Description": "Produces bait on a regular basis. The worms are self-sufficient. / 稳定地提供诱饵。这些虫可以依靠自身维持生存。",
        "MiniForge_Name": "Mini-Forge / 迷你锻造台",
        "Camera_Description": "An old camera mounted on a tripod. / 装在三脚架上的旧相机。",
        "Bongo_Description": "A decorative percussion instrument with a rich sound. / 一种声音浑厚的装饰乐器。",
        "StumpBrazier_Name": "Stump Brazier / 树桩火炬",
        "OilMaker_Description": "Makes gourmet truffle oil. / 生产松露美食油",
        "Incubator_Description": "Hatches eggs into baby chickens and ducks. / 将蛋孵化为小鸡和小鸭。",
        "StoneParrot_Description": "Garden art for your farm. / 适合农场的园艺。",
        "SlimeEggPress_Description": "Compresses 100 pieces of slime into a slime egg. It's a miracle of science! / 将 100 团史莱姆泥压成一个史莱姆蛋。简直是奇迹！",
        "MiniFridge_Description": "Allows you to store additional ingredients for cooking. / 可以储存额外的烹饪原材料。",
        "Furnace_Description": "Turns ore and coal into metal bars. / 将矿石和煤炭转换为金属方块。",
        "WickedStatue_LitEyes_Description": "Something's not right with this statue. / 这个雕像有点不太对劲。",
