        "BigCoop_Description": "Houses 8 coop-dwelling animals. Comes with an incubator. Unlocks ducks. / 可容纳 8 只家禽。附带孵化器。解锁鸭。",
        "Well_Name": "Well / 水井",
        "FishPond_Description": "Raise fish and harvest their produce. Fish multiply over time. / 养鱼并收获水产品。鱼会随着时间的推移而繁殖。",
        "Shed_GeneralName": "Shed / 小屋",
        "DeluxeBarn_Name": "Deluxe Barn / 高级畜棚",
        "Silo_Description": "Allows you to cut and store grass for feed. / 让你把割下来的草料储存起来。",
        "AddedHay": "Added {0} pieces of hay to the silo. / 在筒仓里加了 {0} 片干草。",
        "DeluxeCoop_Description": "Houses 12 coop-dwelling animals. Comes with an auto-feed system. Unlocks rabbits. / 可容纳 12 只家禽。附带自动喂养系统。解锁兔子。",
        "JunimoHut_Name": "Junimo Hut / 祝尼魔屋",
        "Shed_Description": "An empty building. Fill it with whatever you like! The interior can be decorated. / 一栋空的建筑。装入任何你想装的东西！可以装饰内部。",
        "Greenhouse_Name": "Greenhouse / 温室",
        "DesertObelisk_Description": "Warps you to the desert. / 将你传送到沙漠。",
        "CantMill": "Can't be milled / 无法研磨",
        "WaterObelisk_Description": "Warps you to the beach. / 将你传送到海滩。",
        "Greenhouse_Description": "A place to grow crops from any season, year round! / 可全年种植任何季节的作物的地方！",
        "BigBarn_Name": "Big Barn / 大畜棚",
        "SlimeHutch_Description": "Raise up to 20 slimes. Fill water troughs and slimes will create slime balls. / 可饲养 20 只史莱姆。装满饮水槽，史莱姆就会制造史莱姆球。",
        "BigShed_Name": "Big Shed / 大屋子"
      }
    },
