    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Strings/Characters",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "Saloon_goodEvent_2": "Big play! / 干得好！",
        "Phone_Ring_Foreign": "It's a pre-recorded message in a foreign language. You can't understand it at all. / 这是一段用别国语言说的预留录音。你完全听不懂。",
        "MovieTheater_LikeMovie": "{0} seems to be having a good time! / {0}似乎看得很开心！",
        "Saloon_goodEvent_3": "YES! / 漂亮！",
        "Phone_Gus_Open_Rare": "(You hear slurping and chewing sounds on the other end...)#$b#*gulp* ... Uh.. Oh! Well, hello! Hahah... pardon me, I was just tasting today's special, '{0}'. It's delicious. Yes... Yes we're open right now. Come by if you want a taste! *click* / （电话那头传来咀嚼声和喝汤的呼噜声……）#$b#（咕噜）……嗯……啊！你好！哈哈哈，不好意思，我刚才在尝今天的特色菜，{0}，很好吃。对……我们店现在是营业时间。你想吃的话欢迎你的光临！（啪嗒）",
        "MovieInvite_AlreadyInvitedSomeone": "You've already made plans to see a movie with {0} today! / 你今天已经计划好要和{0}看电影了！",
        "Phone_Ring_RoboCaller": "You hear a robotic voice on the other end. # Congratulations. . . You. Have. A. 10,000g. JOJA. Rebate. Waiting. For. You. . . Please. Mail. Your. Credit. Card. Number. To. 133. N. Gunger St. Zuzu. City. To. Receive. Your. Rebate. . . *CLICK* / 电话里传来机械的声音。#恭喜……你有。一份。Joja 的。10,000 金的。返款。未领取……请把。你的。信用卡。号码。邮寄到。祖祖市。冈格尔街。北。133 号。领取。返款……（啪嗒）",
        "MovieInvite_Reject": "Sorry, I'm not in the mood to see a movie right now... / 不好意思，我现在没有心情看电影……",
        "Relative_Mother": "mother / 母亲",
        "Relative_HalfBrother": "half-brother / 同母异父的哥哥",
        "MovieInvite_Reject_Child": "I don't think I'm allowed to see this... / 我家里人大概不让我去看……",
        "WipedMemory": "You're the new farmer, aren't you?#$e#You seem... no. I'm sure we've never met. / 你就是新来那位农场主吧？#$e#你很面熟……不对，我记得从未见过你。",
        "DefaultHorseName": "Grover / 格罗佛",
        "Phone_Clint_Working": "Hello? Yes? Your tool still needs a few more days of work. Check back with me later. *click* / 喂？你好？你的工具还要几天才能做好，过段时间再打过来吧。（啪嗒）",
        "Relative_EldestSon": "eldest son / 长子",
        "Phone_Clint_Open": "Hello? Oh, hey, @. Yup, I'm open for business until 4PM. Er... Okay. Goodbye. *click* / 喂？啊，@，你好。对，我的店开到下午 4 点。呃……好的。再见。（啪嗒）",
        "Relative_Aunt": "aunt / 阿姨",
        "Relative_Daughter": "daughter / 女儿",
        "MovieTheater_ConcessionAlone": "Oh, it looks like you're here by yourself. If you come here with a guest, you can order them a snack. Try it out some time! / 哦，看起来您是独自来的。如果您同一位客人一起来，可以给他们点一份吃的。下次试试！",
        "AbigailInMine2": "Hi @! I made it here without fighting any monsters...  / 嗨，@！我没有和任何怪物交手就到了这里……",
        "Saloon_neutralEvent_3": "Pass the ball! / 传球！",
        "Phone_Pierre_Closed": "Thank you for calling Pierre's General Store. We're closed at the moment, but our hours are 9AM to 5PM. See you then! *beep* / 欢迎致电皮埃尔的杂货店。现在不是营业时间，我们的营业时间是早 9 点到下午 5 点。到时候再见！（嘟嘟）",
        "MovieInvite_Spouse_Harvey": "Movie tickets? Well... yes, I'd love to go with you!$h#$e#It's good to do things like this, I don't want married life to get boring for you! / 这是电影票吗？嗯……好啊，我很乐意跟你一起去！$h#$e#时不时安排这样的活动确实挺好，我不希望婚后生活会让你感到枯燥无聊呢！",
        "MovieInvite_Closed": "The movie theater is closed for the night... / 电影院晚上不开……",
        "MovieTheater_CurrentlyShowing": "A movie is currently being screened, come back again later. / 电影院里正在放电影，请稍后再来。",
        "Phone_Marlon_Open": "Marlon speaking... Did you lose something in the mines again? Yes, yes... I'm willing to fetch it... for a price. / 我是马龙……你又在矿井里丢失东西了吗？好，好……我可以去拿……不过要收费。",
        "MovieTheater_ClosedFestival": "The movie theater is closed for the festival. / 节日期间电影院暂停营业。",
        "Phone_Clint_Open_Rare": "Hello? Yes, yes, I'm open until 4pm. Gotta go. *click* / 喂？对对，我的店开到下午 4 点。就这样。（咔嗒）^Hello? Oh... @... Your voice sounds really nice over the phone... Uh... Okay. Understood. I'm open until 4pm. *slam*$4 / 喂？哦……@……你的声音在电话里真好听……啊……好的，我知道了。我的店开到下午 4 点。（砰）$4",
        "Phone_Ring_Lewis": "Hey, @. #$b#I just wanted to check up on you and see if %farm Farm is doing well.#$b#$y 'How's everything going?_Good! I really feel at home here._Good to hear. *I think I can speak for everyone in saying that we really value your presence in the community.*Your Grandfather would be really proud of what you've accomplished. *Well, I'll let you get back to your work. Goodbye!_Good! The farm is very productive._Good to hear! *Your farm has really boosted the local economy, which is good for everyone. We all appreciate your hard work! *I think it's safe to say that your Grandfather would be really proud of what you've accomplished.*Well, I'll let you get back to your work. Goodbye!_Not so good..._Oh... I'm sorry to hear that. $s*Uh... Keep working hard and I'm sure things will improve... *Well... I'll let you get back to it, then... Okay? Talk to you later. Bye. $s_I know your secret, Lewis._What's that? I think the line cut out... I can't hear a thing. Alright, well I guess I'll hang up then. Bye.$3' / @，你好。#$b#我只是想跟你通个电话，也看看%farm农场经营得怎么样。#$b#$y '一切都好吗？_很不错！我在这里很自在！_那我就放心了。*你在我们的社区里真的很重要，我相信大家都这么觉得。*你的祖父一定会对你的成就感到自豪。*嗯，我就不耽误你的活了。再见！_挺好的！农作物长势很好。_那我就放心了！*你的农场确实促进了我们这里的经济发展，对大家都有好处。我们都很感谢你的辛勤工作！*我觉得你的祖父应该会对你所取得的成就感到自豪。*嗯，我就不耽误你的活了。再见！_不算很好……_啊……那挺糟糕的，不过没关系。$s*呃……继续努力，我相信会好起来的……*嗯，我就不耽误你的活了……如何？之后再聊吧。再见。$s_我知道你的秘密，刘易斯。_你说什么？电话是不是坏了，我什么也没听见……算了，那我就挂掉吧。再见。$3'",
        "MovieInvite_Spouse_Sam": "Nice! You got us tickets? You're the best! I'll wait for you at the theater.$h / 好哇！你给我们都买了票吗？你最棒了！那我就去电影院等你咯！$h",
        "MovieTheater_AlreadySeen": "You've already seen a movie this week. / 你这周已经看过一次电影了。",
        "Leo_Memory_Answer_Yes": "Remind me / 什么事情？",
        "MovieTheater_AfterMovie": "{0} is engaging in lively discussion about the film. / {0}在兴味盎然地讨论电影的事情。",
        "Phone_CheckToolCost": "Check tool upgrade costs / 确认工具升级费用",
        "Phone_Clint_Closed": "You've reached Clint's answering machine. I'm not available right now... My business hours are from 9AM to 4PM. *beep* / 现在转到克林特的电话答录机。我现在不在……我的店铺营业时间是从上午 9 点到下午 4 点。（嘟嘟）",
        "Phone_Robin_Workout": "Hey, it's Robin. I'm out of the house today for my weekly aerobics club... Sorry! *beep* / 嘿，我是罗宾。我今天出门参加每周的有氧健身俱乐部活动了……抱歉！（嘟嘟）",
        "MovieInvite_Spouse_Shane": "Oh, you want to see a show, huh? Buy me a snack and it's a deal, hehe...$h#$e#I'll meet you there. / 噢，你想去看表演了？给我买零食我就去，哈哈……$h#$e#我们到那边再见吧。",
        "Phone_Gus_Festival": "Hello, this is Gus from the Stardrop Saloon. We're closed for the day. *beep* / 你好，我是星之果实餐吧的格斯。店内今天不营业。（嘟嘟）",
        "Phone_Marnie_Closed": "Hello, you've reached Marnie's Ranch. My business hours are from 9AM to 4PM. Please come visit me then. *beep* / 你好，这里是玛妮的牧场。牧场的营业时间是早 9 点到下午 4 点。请在这个时间段内来。（嘟嘟）",
        "Relative_LittleBabyGirl": "little baby-girl / 小女婴",
        "MovieTheater_ConcessionPurchased": "You wanted the {0}, right? We'll deliver it to {1}'s seat once the movie starts! / 您要点{0}，是吗？电影开始后我们会把它送到{1}的座位！",
        "Phone_Pierre_Festival": "Thank you for calling Pierre's General Store. We're closed today in observance of the festival. *beep* / 感谢致电皮埃尔的杂货店。为庆祝节日，店内暂停营业。（嘟嘟）",
        "Saloon_badEvent_2": "Booo! / 哎呦！",
        "AbigailInMine3": "Hey! It's a relief to see you down here...$h#$e#Um... don't tell my Dad I'm here, okay?$9 / 嘿！看到你在这里，真让人宽慰……$h#$e#呃……不要告诉我爸爸我在这里，好吗？$9",
        "Phone_Ring_Bear": "*sniff* *sniff*$2#$b#HoOoOoOoOoO!$3#$b#... Is that you? #$b# *grunt*... I have some of that good sauce still, friend.#$b#It's making me very, very happy. *snort*$1#$b#Just want to thank you... bye bye friend. *click* / （嗅嗅）$2#$b#吼哦哦哦哦哦哦！$3#$b#……是你吗？#$b#（呼噜）……那个什么酱我还留着一点呢，朋友。#$b#那个很好吃，我特别特别开心。（呼噜）$1#$b#我只是想说声谢谢……拜拜，朋友。（啪嗒）",
        "MovieInvite_Invited_Child": "A movie? Yay! Let's meet up at the theater! / 看电影？耶！那我们在电影院碰头吧！",
        "Divorced_bouquet": "This... Are you trying to hurt me even more?$s / 这……你是嫌伤害得我不够深吗？$s",
        "Henchman4": "Mmmm... that looks fresh, but no thanks... why don't you have it? / 嗯……好新鲜，不过我不能接受……不如你自己用吧？",
        "Saloon_goodEvent_0": "Score!! / 进球！！",
        "FallbackDialogueForError": "... / ……",
        "Leo_Memory_6497423": "When we talked about your home? / 我们谈到你的家的时候？",
        "MovieInvite_NoTheater": "{0} looks puzzled... / {0}看起来很疑惑……",
        "Relative_YoungestBoy": "youngest boy / 最小的男孩",
        "AbigailInMineFlute": "%Abigail is lost in her music... / %阿比盖尔正沉醉在她的音乐里。",
        "MovieInvite_Festival": "The movie theater isn't open on festival days! / 节日期间电影院不开放！",
        "MovieInvite_Invited_Sandy": "Ooh.. I'd love to join you.  You go on ahead and I'll meet you there, honey... I have to freshen up! / 哦哦……我很乐意跟你去。你先去吧，我到那里找你，亲爱的……我要打扮一下！",
        "Phone_HangUp": "(Hang up) / （挂断）",
        "Relative_YoungestSon": "youngest son / 老幺",
        "MovieTheater_Closed": "The movie theater is closed. / 电影院目前暂停营业。",
        "Phone_Clint_Festival": "Hey, this is Clint. I'm taking the day off today. *beep* / 嘿，我是克林特。我今天休息。（嘟嘟）",
        "MovieInvite_Spouse_Leah": "Oh, a movie? Sure, sounds fun.... It'll be like we're dating again, hehe.$h#$e#I'll meet you at the theater. / 噢，看电影吗？好呀，听起来很有趣……感觉像是回到我们还在谈恋爱的时候了，嘿嘿。$h#$e#那我们到电影院再见啦。",
        "MovieInvite_InvitedBySomeoneElse": "Sorry, I've already got plans to see a movie today, but maybe you can join us there? / 抱歉，我今天已经计划要好演电影了，不过你也可以跟我们一起去，如何？",
        "MovieInvite_Invited_Krobus": "Oh? I normally hide myself from humans...#$b#But I have an idea... I'll meet you at the theater later. / 哦？我一般不去人多的地方……#$b#不过我想到了一个主意……之后跟你在影院见面吧。",
        "MovieTheater_WatchWithFriendPrompt": "Would you like to spend your movie ticket to see a movie with {0}? / 你要用你的电影票和{0}一起看电影吗？",
        "MovieInvite_Spouse_Maru": "Oh! You planned a date night for us? $h#$b#I'd love to go! I'll see you at the theater.$h / 噢！你为我们安排了一次约会吗？ $h#$b#我很愿意去！我们之后在电影院碰头吧。$h",
        "Divorced_gift": "I don't want your gift.$a / 我才不要你的礼物。$a",
        "Phone_Robin_Open": "Hello? Hey! Yes, I'm currently open for business... please swing by before 5PM if you need anything! *click* $h / 喂？啊！对，现在是营业时间……如果您需要买东西，请在下午 5 点之前过来！（啪嗒）$h",
        "Henchman5": "*sniff*...*sniff*...#$b#That smell...#$b#I can't resist... Gimme that!$h / *嗅嗅*……*嗅嗅*……#$b#这味道……#$b#抗拒不了了……快给我！$h",
        "MovieTheater_LoveConcession_Female": "{0} is really enjoying her {1}! / {0}真的很享受吃她的{1}！",
        "Henchman1": "Gweee-ah!! Human!#$b#...You want to pass? I'm sorry, this is private property.$s / 咿哈！！人类！#$b#……你想路过这里？不好意思，这是私有领地。$s",
        "Henchman3": "You're offering this to me? Hmm... no thanks.$s / 这是送我的？嗯……我不能接受，谢啦。$s",
        "MovieTheater_LoveConcession": "{0} is really enjoying their {1}! / {0}真的很享受吃{1}！",
        "Saloon_neutralEvent_0": "C'mon... / 加把劲啊……",
        "MovieInvite_CantInvite": "You cannot invite {0} to the movies. / 你不能邀请{0}看电影。",
        "Relative_LittleBrother": "little brother / 小弟弟",
        "MovieInvite_Invited": "A movie? Sure. I'll meet you at the theater. / 看电影？好呀。电影院见。",
        "Phone_Robin_Festival": "Hey, it's Robin. I'm taking the day off today. Sorry for the inconvenience! *beep* / 嘿，我是罗宾。我今天休息一天，很抱歉给您带来不便！（嘟嘟）",
        "MovieTheater_WatchAlonePrompt": "Would you like to spend your movie ticket to see a movie by yourself? / 你要用你的电影票一个人看电影吗？",
        "Relative_Husband": "husband / 丈夫",
        "MovieTheater_LoveMovie": "{0} is absolutely enthralled...! / {0}真的被深深吸引了……！",
        "AbigailInMineFirst": "Hey, @. Surprised? ...I finally found the courage to come down here.#$b#I felt scared at first, but I pushed through.#$b#I feel much more confident now. This is actually really fun!$h / 嘿，@。惊喜吗？……我终于鼓起勇气来这里。#$b#起初我感到害怕，但是我做到了。#$b#我现在感觉更加自信了。事实上，这挺有趣的！$h",
        "MovieTheater_ConcessionAfterMovie": "So, how was the movie? / 电影怎么样？",
        "Phone_Marnie_Open_Rare": "Lew...? Hah... Heyyy! Yup, I'm open right now. *bahhh*. That sound? Oh, it's one of my goats. Please come by if you need anything! *click* $4 / 刘……？啊啊啊……你好呀！对的，店现在开着呢。（咩咩咩）声音？啊，是我的羊。你需要什么的话欢迎过来选购！（啪嗒）$4",
        "Saloon_neutralEvent_1": "So close! / 差一点！",
        "Phone_Gus_Closed": "Hello, this is Gus from the Stardrop Saloon. We're currently closed, but please come by later if you'd like to try our daily special, '{0}'! *beep* / 你好，我是星之果实餐吧的格斯。店里现在不是营业时间，如果你想品尝每日特色菜“{0}”的话还请稍后再来！（嘟嘟）",
        "Relative_Mom": "mom / 妈妈",
        "MovieInvite_FarmerAlreadySeen": "I don't feel like going to the movies again just yet... / 我暂时还没有兴趣再去看电影……",
        "MovieInvite_Invited_Wizard": "Hmmph... Very well. I will join you for this... spectacle. / 嗯……好的。我会跟你一起去看这个……精彩的表演。",
        "Phone_SelectOption": "Please make a selection: / 请选择：",
        "Phone_Marnie_Open": "Hello? Oh, hi @! Yes, my shop is open until 4:00 PM today. Hope to see you soon! *click* / 喂？啊，@，你好！对，我的店今天开到下午 4 点。欢迎来光顾！（啪嗒）",
        "Leo_Memory_6497421": "When we talked about birds? / 我们谈到鸟儿的时候？",
        "MovieTheater_LeavePrompt": "Are you sure you want to leave the theater without seeing the movie? / 你确定没看电影就要离开影院吗？",
        "Phone_Ring_HatMouse": "You hear a squeaky voice on the other end: # Heyo poke! Me sell gud hats. Please come, n' bring coines, poke. Me like coines. *click* / 电话里传来尖细的声音：#嘿哟波克！窝卖吼帽子。波克，来吧，带点金闭。窝爱金闭。（啪嗒）",
        "MovieTheater_DislikeConcession_Male": "{0} hasn't touched his {1} at all... / {0}完全没碰过他的{1}……",
        "MovieInvite_Spouse_Penny": "A movie ticket? Yes, I'd love to go with you! I'll meet you at the theater, honey.$h / 这是电影票？好啊，我很乐意跟你一起去！亲爱的，那我们到电影院再见啦。$h",
        "Phone_Gus_Closed_NoDishOfTheDay": "Hello, this is Gus from the Stardrop Saloon. We're currently closed. Please stop in between 12PM and 12AM if you'd like some of our delicious food and drink. *beep* / 你好，我是星之果实餐吧的格斯。店里现在不是营业时间。如果你想品尝我们店的美味食物与饮品，请在晚 12 点到中午 12 点间过来。（嘟嘟）",
        "Leo_Memory_Answer_No": "I'm busy / 我很忙",
        "Relative_Sister": "sister / 姐姐",
        "PetLovesYou": "{0} loves you. < / {0}爱你。",
        "JunimoTextAboveHead1": "Junimo! / 祝尼魔！",
        "Saloon_neutralEvent_4": "Go for it! / 上啊！",
        "Saloon_badEvent_3": "Ugh / 呃啊",
        "MovieTheater_DislikeConcession": "{0} hasn't touched their {1} at all... / {0}完全没碰过它的{1}……",
        "MovieTheater_Concession": "Welcome to the concessions stand! Would you like to order a snack for your guest? / 欢迎来到小卖部！您想给您的客人点一些零食吗？",
        "Phone_CheckAnimalPrices": "Check livestock prices / 确认牲畜价格",
        "Relative_HalfSister": "half-sister / 同母异父的妹妹",
        "MovieTheater_BoxOfficeClosed": "The box office is empty. / 售票处无人。",
        "Leo_Memory_6497428": "When I decided to move? / 我决定要移居的时候？",
        "Relative_Grandma": "grandma / 奶奶",
        "Phone_Pierre_Open": "Pierre's General Store! Oh, hello, @! Yes, I'm open until 5pm today. Please come by for great deals on seeds and produce! Goodbye. *click* / 这里是皮埃尔的杂货店！啊，@，你好！对，我们店今天开到下午 5 点。过来就能享受种子和农产品的超值价！拜拜。（啪嗒）",
        "MovieTheater_LikeConcession": "{0} is enjoying their {1}. / {0}吃{1}吃得很开心。",
        "KrobusDarkTalisman": "What's that... you're looking for a dark talisman?#$b#...Hmmm. Now that you mention it, I did have one in my possession not too long ago.#$b#Unfortunately, I dropped it while exploring that tunnel in the far corner.#$b#Things started heating up in there, so I left in a hurry and sealed the entrance.#$b#You seem pretty sturdy, though... So I'll open it back up for you. Just be careful, okay? / 那是什么……你在找黑暗护身符？#$b#……嗯。你这么一说，我倒是记得曾经有过个护身符。#$b#不过不久前我在勘察那边那条地道的时候弄丢了。#$b#当时地道里开始升温，所以我就匆匆离开了，走之前还把入口给封了。#$b#你看着挺精壮的，应该能对付得了里面的牛鬼蛇神。我可以为你重新打开入口。你自己小心点，懂吗？",
        "MovieInvite_Invited_Dwarf": "A moo-what? Well, I'm sure I'll like it! I'd be happy to go with you. / 电什么？算了，我肯定会喜欢的！我很乐意跟你一起去。",
        "MovieInvite_Spouse_Abigail": "A movie? Sure, sounds fun! I'll meet you at the theater.$h#$e#I hope it's an exciting one. / 电影吗？好呀，听起来很有趣！那我们到电影院再见啦$h#$e#希望是一部刺激的电影呢。",
        "Phone_Gus_Open_NoDishOfTheDay": "Hello? Hi @! Yup, we're open right now. Hope to see you soon! *click*$h / 喂？@，你好！没错，我们店开着呢。赶紧来吧！（啪嗒）$h",
        "MovieInvite_AlreadySeen": "Sorry, I've already seen a movie this week... / 抱歉，这周我已经看过一次电影了……",
        "Phone_Clint_Working_OneDay": "Hey... Your tool will be ready for pickup tomorrow. I gotta get back to work now. *clank* *clank* *click* / 嘿……你的工具明天就做好了。现在我得回去工作了。（当啷）（当啷）（啪嗒）",
        "KrobusDarkTalisman_elsewhere": "What's that... you're looking for a dark talisman?#$b#...Hmmm. Now that you mention it, I did have one in my possession not too long ago.#$b#Unfortunately, I dropped it while exploring a tunnel in the sewers.#$b#Things started heating up in there, so I left in a hurry and sealed the entrance.#$b#You seem pretty sturdy, though... So I'll open it back up for you. Just be careful, okay? / 那是啥……你在找黑暗护身符吗？#$b#……唔。说起来，我想起我最近的存货里确实有一个。#$b#可惜的是我在探索下水道的通路的时候把它弄丢了。#$b#那里面闹得挺厉害的，所以我匆匆离开，把门口堵上了。#$b#不过你看着蛮结实的……那我就帮你重新打开吧。记得要小心，好吗？",
        "JunimoThankYou2": "A gift! / 一份礼物！",
        "MovieInvite_Spouse_Elliott": "Yes, my dear, I'd love to see a movie with you! I'll meet you at the theater. / 当然了，我亲爱的，我很乐意跟你一起看电影！那我们到电影院再见啦。",
        "Henchman2": "I'm sorry, but I can't let you pass... I'd lose my job. / 对不起，不能让你通过……我可不想丢掉饭碗。",
        "Phone_Ring_Vincent": "Hello?#$b#Um... Uhhh... This is Vincent.$3#$b#... $3#$b#Um... Do you have any piggies on your farm?$h#$b#...$3#$b#Okay I gotta go! *click* $3 / 喂？#$b#呃……啊……我是文森特。$3#$b#……$3#$b#嗯……你的农场里有小猪吗？$h#$b#……$3#$b#好的，我得走了！（啪嗒）$3",
        "JunimoThankYou1": "Thank you! / 非常感谢！",
        "JunimoTextAboveHead2": "Star! / 星星！",
        "Relative_Son": "son / 儿子",
        "Henchman6": "Thanks. / 谢啦。",
        "Relative_Dad": "dad / 爸爸",
        "Phone_CheckSeedStock": "Check store inventory / 确认商店库存",
        "MovieTheater_LikeConcession_Female": "{0} is enjoying her {1}. / {0}吃她的{1}吃得很开心。",
        "Phone_Gus_Open": "Hello? Hi @! Yes... today's special is: '{0}'! We're open right now, so feel free to come on in for a taste. *click* / 喂？@，你好！对……今天的特色菜是：{0}！我们店现在是营业时间，所以你可以过来吃吃看，不用客气。（啪嗒）",
        "Phone_Ring_Cursed": "You place the receiver to your ear, and are met with a roiling, abrasive static. # But wait... beneath it all, you can make out something else... an otherworldly voice... # 'Y-O-U H-A-V-E F-O-R-S-A-K-E-N U-S' / 你把听筒放在耳边，只听见粗糙混乱的静电声。#等等……掩盖在杂乱的声音下，似乎能听到什么……是灵异的声音……#“你——抛——弃——了——我——们——”",
        "AbigailInMine1": "Eep!$7#$b#Hahah! You scared me! I didn't expect to see another person down here!$h#$e#Sorry, I'm all sweaty from excitement... / 哎呀！$7#$b#哈哈！你吓到我了！我没想到会在这里遇到另一个人！$h#$e#对不起，我兴奋得大汗淋漓……",
        "Saloon_goodEvent_1": "Wooo! / 哇哦！",
        "Relative_Nephew": "nephew / 外甥",
        "AbigailInMine4": "Hey! Exploring the mines on a rainy day, huh? Me too!$h / 嘿！要在雨天里探索矿井，是吗？我也是！$h",
        "Saloon_badEvent_0": "Arrgh! / 啊啊啊！",
        "MovieInvite_Spouse_Haley": "Oooh... date night, huh? Let me just freshen up a little and I'll meet you at the theater.$h / 哎呦……今晚要出去约会呀？我得去稍微打扮一下，我们到电影院再见啦。$h",
        "Phone_Robin_Open_Rare": "Hello? Oh, hi @! *BANG*... Um, one sec... (Muffled Voice: Honey, could you close the door? I'm trying to run a business here.)... Sorry! Yes, I'm open until 5pm today. See you later! *click*  / 喂？啊，@，你好！（砰！）……呃，请稍等……（沉闷的声音：亲爱的，你能把门关上吗？我这边有工作要做。）……抱歉！对的，小店开到下午 5 点。回见！（啪嗒）",
        "Phone_SelectNumber": "Please select a number: / 请选择号码：",
        "Phone_Ring_Pierre": "Hey, @. It's me, Pierre. #$b#How are you doing? Good? That's good.#$b#Well, I just wanted to say that I appreciate your business. And I'd like to remind you that Pierre's General Store carries *the finest* seeds and produce anywhere.#$b#I hope to see you in the store very soon. Bye! *click*  / @，你好。是我，皮埃尔。#$b#你最近怎么样？过得不错？那就好。#$b#嗯，我只是想感谢你这么照顾我的生意。而且我想提醒你一下，皮埃尔杂货店里都是最~好的种子和农产品。#$b#希望你能快快来光顾我的商店。拜拜！（啪嗒） ",
        "Phone_CheckBuildingCost": "Check building upgrade costs / 确认建筑升级费用",
        "Relative_Grandpa": "grandpa / 爷爷",
        "Saloon_goodEvent_4": "Good job! / 好样的！",
        "MovieTheater_AfterMovieAlone": "{0} is thinking silently about the film. / {0}在安静地想电影的事情。",
        "Saloon_neutralEvent_2": "Let's go! / 走起来！",
        "Saloon_badEvent_4": "Not good. / 不像样。",
        "Phone_Robin_Working_OneDay": "Hey, it's Robin. I'll be out of the house until tomorrow finishing up a project. *beep* / 嘿，我是罗宾。我出门去完成一个项目，明天才回来。（嘟嘟）",
        "MovieInvite_Spouse_Sebastian": "Oh, you want to go to the movies? Sounds pretty good. I'll meet you there.$h / 噢，你想去看电影？听起来挺不错的，我们到那边再见吧。$h",
        "Phone_Robin_Working": "Hey, it's Robin. I'll be busy for the next few days working on a project. *beep* / 嘿，我是罗宾。最近几天我在忙着做一个项目。（嘟嘟）",
        "MovieTheater_DislikeConcession_Female": "{0} hasn't touched her {1} at all... / {0}完全没碰过她的{1}……",
        "MovieTheater_DislikeMovie": "{0} is dozing off... / {0}快要睡着了……",
        "MovieTheater_LikeConcession_Male": "{0} is enjoying his {1}. / {0}吃他的{1}吃得很开心。",
        "Phone_Robin_Closed": "Hey, it's Robin. My business hours are from 9AM to 5PM. Please come by then if you need anything! *beep* / 嘿，我是罗宾。本店营业时间是上午 9 点到下午 5 点。如果需要购物的话请在营业时间内来！（嘟嘟）",
        "Leo_Memory": "Hey... I was just thinking about that time, back on the island... Do you remember? / 嘿……我正想着我们当时在岛上的事情……你还记得吗？",
        "Phone_Marnie_ClosedDay": "Hello, you've reached Marnie's Ranch. My shop is closed today. / 你好，这里是玛妮的牧场。小店今天休息。",
        "Phone_Marlon_NoDeathItems": "What's that? You haven't lost anything in the mines? Okay. Sounds like you don't need my help, then. Take care. *click* / 什么？你根本没在矿井里丢东西？行吧。那你大概不需要我的帮助。好了，多保重。（啪嗒）",
        "MovieTheater_LoveConcession_Male": "{0} is really enjoying his {1}! / {0}真的很享受吃他的{1}！",
        "MovieInvite_Spouse_Emily": "A movie ticket! You know, I was thinking about the movies all day. You must've read my mind! $h#$e#I'll meet you at the theater. / 是电影票呀！要知道，我这一整天都在想电影的事情呢，你一定是读了我的心吧！$h#$e#那我们到电影院再见啦。",
        "Phone_CheckHouseCost": "Check house upgrade cost / 确认房屋升级费用",
        "Relative_Wife": "wife / 妻子",
        "MovieInvite_Spouse_Alex": "Hey, sounds fun! I've been wanting to see this one... and I'd rather see it with you!#$b#I'll meet you at the theater. / 哎，听起来很有趣嘛！我想看这部电影很久了……而且我更想跟你一起看！#$b#那我们到电影院再见啦。",
        "Relative_Niece": "niece / 侄女",
        "MovieTheater_NoTicket": "You cannot enter the theater without a ticket! / 没有电影票不能进入电影院！",
        "AbigailInMine0": "Hey! I made it pretty far, didn't I?$h / 嘿！我挺成功的，不是吗？$h",
        "Phone_Pierre_Open_Rare": "Abigail! Your guinea pig is loose again! Come here *right now* and take care of this! $3#$b#Oh! Uh... Hello? Thank you for calling. Y... Yes, we're open until 5PM. Goodbye. *click*$4 / 阿比盖尔！你的豚鼠又跑出来了！立！马！给我过来处理一下！$3#$b#啊！呃……你好？感谢你的致电……对，对，我们店开到下午 5 点。再见！（啪嗒）$4",
        "Relative_Grandson": "grandson / 孙子",
        "PierreStockListDialogue": "Oh, wow! It's my old stock list! I've been searching everywhere for this thing.$h#$b#Let me see... yup! It's all still here.#$b#With these order codes, I can expand my stock to include seeds from all seasons, year round!#$b#Thanks so much for bringing this back to me, @.$h / 哇！这是我以前的库存清单！我一直在到处找它。$h#$b#我看看……没错！都还在上面。#$b#有了这些订单码，我就可以全年售卖四季的种子了！#$b#@，非常感谢你把它还给我。$h",
        "MovieInvite_Invited_Rude": "A movie? Yeah, whatever, sounds good. See you at the theater... / 看电影？啊，可以吧，听起来不错。那就电影院见……",
        "Saloon_badEvent_1": "Noo! / 不！！",
        "NameYourHorse": "Name Your Horse / 给你的马起名",
        "Phone_Marlon_AlreadyRecovering": "Hello?... Yep, I'm going to fetch your item tonight. You can relax. No need to keep calling! *click* / 喂？……对，我今晚就去把你的东西拿回来。别担心，不用一直给我打电话！（啪嗒）"
      }
    },
