        "Mines_Fallen": "You fell {0} levels. / 你掉了 {0} 层。",
        "Club_ClubSeller_No": "No way! / 没门！",
        "BeachNightMarket_GiftGiverEnjoy": "Merchant: Mmm... smells great, doesn't it? / 商人：嗯……闻起来很香，不是吗？",
        "AnimalShop_Marnie_Animals": "Purchase Animals / 购买动物",
        "IslandSecret_Event_BirdieFinished": "tropical_island_day_ambient/-1000 -1000/farmer 20 58 3/removeQuest 130/skippable/addTemporaryActor Birdie 32 32 17 58 3 true/animate Birdie false true 1000 8 9/pause 1000/viewport 18 58 clamp true/pause 2300/playMusic none/animate farmer true true 100 35/addObject 19 58 870/playSound sandyStep/pause 800/stopAnimation farmer/playFramesAhead 3/stopAnimation Birdie/extendSourceRect Birdie reset/warp Birdie 18 58/move Birdie 0 -1 2/move Birdie 1 0 2/pause 500/jump Birdie/pause 500/playMusic desolate/speak Birdie \"It's his...$s\"/emote Birdie 20/pause 1200/playSound coin/removeObject 19 58/showFrame Birdie 20/pause 2500/speak Birdie \"Heh... It still has his smell, after all these years...#$b#...that familiar, putrid funk...$h\"/pause 300/faceDirection farmer 2 true/playSound croak/animate farmer false false 350 104 105 104 105 104 105/pause 1000/faceDirection farmer 3/speak Birdie \"You know... It's been a lonely life here, child... but I don't regret it at all.#$b#I'm doin' right by my old man... and we'll be together again some day soon... hehe\"/pause 500/stopAnimation Birdie/move Birdie 0 1 3/playMusic tropical_island_day_ambient/faceDirection Birdie 1/quickQuestion #It's an honorable thing to do.#He's gone. You should live your life.(break)speak Birdie \"You have great wisdom, child.#$b#And you've brought me great peace... this locket will comfort me for the rest of my days.$h\"(break)emote Birdie 28\\speak Birdie \"An old woman like me? I think it's too late, dear...$s#$b#Besides... I like it here! It's relaxing and beautiful. And I have an endless supply of fresh fish, oysters, and monkey meat. Hehehe.$h#$b#...I'm kidding about the monkey meat.\"/pause 1000/speak Birdie \"Now... how can I repay you for this?\"/jump Birdie/pause 500/speak Birdie \"Oh... How about I teach you a special recipe... Something I discovered in the many years I've spent here.\"/pause 1000/playSound reward/addCraftingRecipe Fairy Dust/message \"Learned to craft 'Fairy Dust'.\"/pause 1000/fork gotBirdieReward Strings\\\\Locations:alreadyGotNuts true/speak Birdie \"You can take these, too...\"/awardFestivalPrize birdieReward true/pause 1000/speak Birdie \"Though you're a stranger, you went out of your way to help an old lady.#$b#Bless your heart!$h\"/emote Birdie 20/emote farmer 32/pause 1000/end / tropical_island_day_ambient/-1000 -1000/farmer 20 58 3/removeQuest 130/skippable/addTemporaryActor Birdie 32 32 17 58 3 true/animate Birdie false true 1000 8 9/pause 1000/viewport 18 58 clamp true/pause 2300/playMusic none/animate farmer true true 100 35/addObject 19 58 870/playSound sandyStep/pause 800/stopAnimation farmer/playFramesAhead 3/stopAnimation Birdie/extendSourceRect Birdie reset/warp Birdie 18 58/move Birdie 0 -1 2/move Birdie 1 0 2/pause 500/jump Birdie/pause 500/playMusic desolate/speak Birdie \"这是他的……$s\"/emote Birdie 20/pause 1200/playSound coin/removeObject 19 58/showFrame Birdie 20/pause 2500/speak Birdie \"呵……这么多年过去了，这上面还有他的味道……#$b#……我再熟悉不过的腐烂恶臭……$h\"/pause 300/faceDirection farmer 2 true/playSound croak/animate farmer false false 350 104 105 104 105 104 105/pause 1000/faceDirection farmer 3/speak Birdie \"孩子……在这里过日子确实是非常孤独的。但我完全不后悔。#$b#我就在我的老头子身边……呵呵，我们马上就能又在一起了……\"/pause 500/stopAnimation Birdie/move Birdie 0 1 3/playMusic tropical_island_day_ambient/faceDirection Birdie 1/quickQuestion #你这么做值得尊敬。#他已经死了，你得有你自己的生活。(break)speak Birdie \"你很聪明，孩子。#$b#你带给了我莫大的安宁……我的余生全因这块吊坠得到抚慰。$h\"(break)emote Birdie 28\\speak Birdie \"像我这样的老女人吗？我觉得已经太迟了，孩子……$s#$b#而且……我喜欢这里！这里令人放松，风景迷人，而且还有吃不完的鲜鱼、牡蛎，还有猴子肉。呵呵呵。$h#$b#……猴子肉是开玩笑的。\"/pause 1000/speak Birdie \"现在……我该如何回报你呢？\"/jump Birdie/pause 500/speak Birdie \"啊……给你传授一份特别的制作方法如何，这是我在这待了这么多年研究出来的。\"/pause 1000/playSound reward/addCraftingRecipe Fairy Dust/message \"已学会制作“仙尘”。\"/pause 1000/fork gotBirdieReward Strings\\\\Locations:alreadyGotNuts true/speak Birdie \"这些也给你……\"/awardFestivalPrize birdieReward true/pause 1000/speak Birdie \"虽然你一开始不认识我这老婆子，还是尽全力帮助了我。#$b#为你的善心献上祝福！$h\"/emote Birdie 20/emote farmer 32/pause 1000/end",
        "ManorHouse_LedgerBook_SharedWallets_SeparateQuestion": "Split the funds of each farmer? Tonight, the money will be divided evenly. If you change your mind, come back here before night's end. / 要分配每个农民的资金吗？今晚，钱会被平均分配。要是你改变了主意，请在天亮前回来。",
        "ChallengeShrine_NotYetHard": "         --Shrine Of Challenge-- / ——挑战之神庙——^Dispel the ancient magi-seal of protection, allowing powerful monsters to ascend from the deep? / 要解除古老的魔法封印，让强大的怪物从深处涌现吗？",
        "FarmHouse_SpouseAttacked7": "Yuck! / 呸！",
        "SkullCave_SkullDoor_Locked": "The door is locked. / 门上锁了。",
        "Blacksmith_Clint_Upgrade": "Upgrade Tools / 升级工具",
        "MineCart_Destination_BusStop": "Bus Stop / 巴士站",
        "IslandSouth_ResortOpenSign": "The beach resort is open. Temporarily close it down tomorrow? / 海滩度假村正在营业中。明天要暂停营业吗？",
        "Desert_SandDragon_Initial": "Its maw gapes at the desert sun. Even in death, it yearns for a taste. / 它张着大嘴，对着沙漠太阳。即使死后也贪得无厌。",
        "ScienceHouse_Renovation_CloseBedroom": "Close Bedroom/Builds a wall separating your bedroom and the entrance room./Select an area for the renovation. / 封闭卧室/在您的卧室和门厅之间建一堵墙。/选择装修区域。",
        "Saloon_Arcade_PK_NewGame+": "Press button for a more difficult journey... / 按下按钮以开始更艰辛的旅程……",
        "BeachNightMarket_GiftGiverClosed": "Merchant: The night market starts at 5pm... visit me then for a free cup of coffee!  / 商人：夜市从下午 5 时开始……到时候来我这里喝杯免费的咖啡！",
        "Beach_Mariner_PlayerNoRelationship": "Old Mariner: I've got this old amulet to sell... but somethin' tells me yer not ready for it, {0}. / 老水手：我这里有个古老的护身符要出售……但直觉告诉我，你尚且不需要用到它，{0}。",
        "HaleyHouse_EmilyRoomObject": "There's a tape inside: 'Freeform Dance Rhythms' / 里面有一盘磁带：‘自由形式舞蹈旋律’",
        "SeedShop_BuyBackpack_Response10000": "Purchase (10,000g) / 购买（10,000金）",
        "Gourmand_Reward": "*Kriibbitt*... Yes... I am very pleased.|Here... This is for you. / 咯哩哩哩……没错……谢谢李。浪我回想起了……过去，很久很久以前，多么美好，小子……|给李……这个送给李。",
        "Mines_ShaftJumpIn": "Jump In / 跳进去",
        "ManorHouse_LAF_FarmhandItemsQuestion": "Who would you like to retrieve items from? / 你要获取谁的物品？",
        "alreadyGotNuts": "pause 50/pause 50/pause 1000/speak Birdie \"Though you're a stranger, you went out of your way to help an old lady.#$b#Bless your heart!$h\"/emote Birdie 20/emote farmer 32/pause 1000/end / pause 50/pause 50/pause 1000/speak Birdie \"虽然你一开始不认识我这老婆子，还是尽全力帮助了我。#$b#为你的善心献上祝福！$h\"/emote Birdie 20/emote farmer 32/pause 1000/end",
        "FarmHouse_SpouseAttacked12": "Gahh! / 嘎！",
        "ManorHouse_LedgerBook_SeparateWallets_MergeQuestion": "Merge the funds of each farmer? Tonight, everyone's money will be combined. If you change your mind, come back here before night's end. / 要合并每个农民的资金吗？今晚，大家的钱会被合并。要是你改变了主意，请在天亮前回来。",
        "Town_SeedShopSign": "- Pierre's General Store -\nNow open 7 days a week From 9am-5pm! / ——皮埃尔商店——\n营业时间为星期一至星期日，早上 9 点至下午 5 点！",
        "ChallengeShrine_OnQiChallenge": "There's a note from Mr. Qi:  / 是齐先生的便条：^ I've temporarily disabled this shrine. Come back tomorrow! / 我暂时关闭了神庙。明天再来吧！",
        "AnimalHouse_Incubator_Hatch_Ostrich": "A new ostrich chick hatched... it's a big one! / 有新的鸵鸟雏鸟孵化出来了……个子好大！",
        "Railroad_TrainComing": "A train is passing through Stardew Valley. / 一列火车正在驶过星露谷。",
        "Desert_SandDragon_MrQiNote": "'You've proven yourself, kid. Check out the pile of lumber next to your house. -Mr. Qi' / “孩子，你证明了自己的实力。去看看你房子旁边的木材堆吧。——齐先生”",
        "NutHint_HutTree": "Bulging very close by... / 很近，有一个隆起……",
        "IslandFieldOffice_Intro_Event": "fieldofficeTentMusic/-1000 -1000/farmer 4 10 0/skippable/addTemporaryActor SafariGuy 16 32 5 4 0 true character/translateName SafariGuy Strings\\NPCNames:ProfessorSnail/viewport 4 6 true/move farmer 0 -2 0/pause 1000/faceDirection SafariGuy 1 true/pause 50/faceDirection SafariGuy 2 true/pause 500/speak SafariGuy \"Ah... Come in!\"/move farmer 2 0 0/move farmer 0 -4 3/faceDirection SafariGuy 1/pause 500/speak SafariGuy \"Welcome to my field office.\"/faceDirection SafariGuy 2/faceDirection farmer 2/showFrame SafariGuy 16/emote SafariGuy 28/pause 500/speak SafariGuy \"As you can see... it's quite empty.$s#$b#Getting stuck in that cave was a huge setback to my project.$s\"/pause 50/showFrame SafariGuy 0/pause 200/faceDirection SafariGuy 1/pause 100/speak SafariGuy \"But that's where you come in! Hee hee...$h\"/faceDirection farmer 3/emote farmer 8/speak SafariGuy \"I'm in the bone business, you see...#$b#Ancient bones, in particular... And this island is full of them.#$b#So if you ever encounter any bones, fossils, or mummified specimens on this island, bring them to my desk, okay? I'll make it worth your while!$h\"/pause 200/faceDirection SafariGuy 1/end / fieldofficeTentMusic/-1000 -1000/farmer 4 10 0/skippable/addTemporaryActor SafariGuy 16 32 5 4 0 true character/translateName SafariGuy Strings\\NPCNames:ProfessorSnail/viewport 4 6 true/move farmer 0 -2 0/pause 1000/faceDirection SafariGuy 1 true/pause 50/faceDirection SafariGuy 2 true/pause 500/speak SafariGuy \"啊……请进！\"/move farmer 2 0 0/move farmer 0 -4 3/faceDirection SafariGuy 1/pause 500/speak SafariGuy \"欢迎来到我的办事处。\"/faceDirection SafariGuy 2/faceDirection farmer 2/showFrame SafariGuy 16/emote SafariGuy 28/pause 500/speak SafariGuy \"如你所见……这里很空。$s#$b#我被困在那个山洞里，所以项目没什么进展。$s\"/pause 50/showFrame SafariGuy 0/pause 200/faceDirection SafariGuy 1/pause 100/speak SafariGuy \"但这就是我叫你来的原因！嘿嘿……$h\"/faceDirection farmer 3/emote farmer 8/speak SafariGuy \"是这样的，我是做骨头生意的……#$b#特别是古代的骨头……这个岛上正好到处都是。#$b#所以说，如果你在这个岛上找到什么骨头、化石、木乃伊标本，请把它们带过来，好吗？我会给你相应的报酬！$h\"/pause 200/faceDirection SafariGuy 1/end",
        "ScienceHouse_Renovation_RemoveCrib": "Remove Crib/Remove the crib from your home./Select a crib to remove. / 移除婴儿床/移除家里的婴儿床。/选择要移除的婴儿床。",
        "NutHint_Arch": "Help man in tent... / 帮助帐篷里的人……",
        "FarmHouse_SpouseAttacked8": "Take that! / 看招！",
        "ArchaeologyHouse_Gunther_Leave": "Leave / 离开",
        "NutHint_VolcanoTreasure": "{0} hidden in fire mountain treasures... / 还有 {0} 个藏在火山宝藏里……",
        "FarmHouse_SpouseAttacked11": "Agh! / 呀！",
        "ScienceHouse_CarpenterMenu_UpgradeCabin": "Upgrade Cabin / 升级联机小屋",
        "Forest_WizardTower_Locked": "It's locked. You can hear someone inside, though. / 虽然上锁了，但你听见里面有人。",
        "WitchHut_EvilShrineCenter": "-Dark Shrine of Memory- / ——记忆之黑暗神殿——^The relationship between you and your ex-spouses will be wiped from memory. It will be like you've never met.^Make an offering of 30,000g? / 你和你配偶之间的一切记忆将会被抹除。就像你们俩从未邂逅过一样。^是否确定献祭 30,000 金？",
        "AdventureGuild_Greeting": "Need something? / 想要什么？",
        "IslandFieldOffice_Welcome_2": "Hey! / 嗨！",
        "ElliottHouse_ElliottBook_Blank": "Blank book / 空白的书",
        "ManorHouse_LedgerBook_SeparateWallets_CancelQuestion": "Cancel merging funds? / 取消合并资金？",
        "Mines_MineElevator_NotWorking": "It doesn't seem to be working... / 似乎无法正常运作……",
        "ScienceHouse_CarpenterMenu_Shop": "Shop / 商店",
        "CommunityCenter_AreaCompletion6": "The last bundle... Farewell... {0}. / 最后一个收集包达成……再见了……{0}。",
        "BoatTunnel_willyText_firstRide": "She looks good as new! / 它焕然一新了！",
        "AdventureGuild_KillList_MagmaSprite": "Magma Sprites / 熔岩精灵",
        "Submarine_AscendQuestion": "Captain: Shall I take us back up? / 艇长：我们要返回水面吗？",
        "IslandFieldOffice_Survey_Notyet": "Not ready / 还没准备好",
        "BoatTunnel_willyText_random1": "Ahoy! / 啊嘿！",
        "WitchHut_EvilShrineLeft": "-Dark Shrine of Selfishness- / ——私欲之黑暗神殿——^Your children will turn into doves and fly away...^Make an offering of one Prismatic Shard? / 你的孩子会变成鸽子飞走……^是否确定献祭一块五彩碎片？",
        "BeachNightMarket_SubmarineInUse": "The submarine is currently in use. Come back later. / 潜艇目前正在使用中。稍后再来。",
        "IslandSouth_ResortClosedSign": "The beach resort is temporarily closed. Open it back up tomorrow? / 海滩度假村暂停营业中。明天要开业吗？",
        "HaleyHouse_DyePot": "An array of brightly colored dyes. / 一组颜色鲜艳的染料。",
        "Club_CalicoJack_Leave": "Leave / 离开",
        "AnimalShop_Marnie_Leave": "Leave / 离开",
        "ScienceHouse_CarpenterMenu_RenovateHouse": "Make House Renovations / 装修房屋",
        "SeedShop_BuyBackpack_ResponseNo": "Not now / 以后再说",
        "Railroad_Box_MrQiNote": "'Well done. Your next task: Place 10 beets inside Mayor's fridge. -Mr. Qi' / “完成得很好。你的下一个任务：将 10 个甜菜放在镇长的冰箱中。——齐先生”",
        "NutHint_StardropPool": "Bathing in the heart of the star... / 浸润在星形的中心……",
        "ManorHouse_LedgerBook_SeparateWallets_HowMuchQuestion": "How much money would you like to send? / 你想要转多少钱？",
        "MineCart_Destination_Quarry": "Quarry / 采石场",
        "ScienceHouse_Carpenter_UpgradeHouse1": "I can increase the size of your house and add a kitchen. It will cost 10,000g and you'll also need to provide me with 450 pieces of wood. Are you interested? / 我可以扩建你的房子并加盖一个厨房。此升级需要消耗 10000 金和 450 块木材。你确定吗？",
        "ScienceHouse_Carpenter_CommunityUpgrade2": "...What's that? You'd like me to add a few shortcuts around the valley? Sure, I can do that! / ……什么？你想让我在山谷周围加几条捷径？我当然能办到！^I'll just need 300,000g... / 我只需要 300,000 金……",
        "WitchHut_EvilShrineLeftInactive": "-Dark Shrine of Selfishness- / ——私欲之黑暗神殿——^The statue stares through you... / 雕像的锐利眼神透视你的身体……",
        "ManorHouse_LedgerBook_SharedWallets_Client": "Pelican Town Ledger Book... The owner of the farm can request the mayor to split the funds of the farmhands. / 鹈鹕镇账目表……农场主可以要求镇长分配农场工人的资金。",
        "FieldOfficeDonated_2": "You've outdone yourself, @. This is one of the most pristine specimens I've ever seen. Thank you!$h / 你真是太棒了，@。这是我见过的保存最完好的标本之一，谢谢你！$h",
        "Town_DwarfGrave_Translated": "     You translate the dwarvish:\n\nStand between the pillars three\nWith gift as precious as the sky:\nA rainbow forged from land, not sea\nThen galaxies will heed your cry.\n / 你翻译了该段矮人语：\n\n站在三根柱子间，\n怀中礼物像天空一样珍贵：\n彩虹从陆地而不是海上升起，\n银河将会听见你的呼唤。 \n",
        "BusStop_BuyTicketToDesert": "Buy a ticket to Calico Desert for {0}g? / 是否确定花费 {0} 金购买前往卡利科沙漠的车票？",
        "ScienceHouse_Carpenter_CommunityUpgrade1": "...What's that? You want to build Pam a house? That's a great idea! / ……那是什么？你想为潘姆建一间房子吗？好主意！^I'll just need 950 wood and 500,000g... / 我只需要 950 块木头和 500,000 金……",
        "ManorHouse_LAF_Check_OrdersUnlocked": "The town's 'Lost and Found' box. You can collect incomplete deliveries from past special orders here. / 镇上的失物招领箱。你可以在这里获取过去没有完成的特别订单中的物品。",
        "AdventureGuild_KillList_Duggies": "Duggies / 掘地虫",
        "Sewer_DogStatue": "-Statue Of Uncertainty- / ——不确定雕像——^The statue can help you change professions.^Make an offering of 10,000g? / 这尊雕像可帮你改变职业。^要价 10,000 金吗？",
        "Farm_GrandpaShrine_DiamondSlot": "There's a diamond-shaped slot in the shrine... was that always there? / 神龛里面有个钻石形槽位……这是本来就存在的吗？",
        "Mines_Shaft": "There's a shaft leading down. / 下面有一个矿井。",
        "NutHint_WestHidden": "{0} hidden in the west... / 还有 {0} 个藏在西边……",
        "IslandFieldOffice_Survey_Failed": "Hmm... I think you should take a break and try doing the survey again tomorrow... / 唔……我觉得你应该休息一下，明天再接着调查……",
        "FieldOfficeDonated_1": "Beautiful! These bones are exactly what I'm looking for. Now, let me clean my magnifying lens... / 完美！这骨头正是我要找的。来，让我擦一下放大镜……",
        "IslandFieldOffice_Welcome_3": "Welcome! / 欢迎！",
        "AnimalHouse_Incubator_Hatch_DinosaurEgg": "A new baby ...lizard?... hatched. / 孵化出了一只小……蜥蜴。",
        "Volcano_ShortcutOut": "Take the shortcut out of the volcano? / 要走捷径离开火山吗？",
        "AdventureGuild_KillList_LineFormat": "{0}/{1} {2} / {0}/{1} {2}",
        "Club_Bouncer_TextAboveHead2": "You little punk... / 你个混蛋……",
        "IslandSouth_ResortOpenWillCloseSign": "The beach resort will temporarily close tomorrow. Keep it open? / 海滩度假村明天将暂停营业。明天要继续营业吗？",
        "Gourmand_Request_2_Success": "*Gurrrp*... Yes... I ate this once, long ago. It gave me a pungent aroma for days...|...Reminds me of Papa, when I was just a tadpole...|Heh... I could take a bite, and produce that poignant odor once more...|...But, I won't. / 呼噜噜……没错……窝要再次一次辣个东西。浪窝的口气 biu 臭……|……浪窝想起窝爹，窝辣时候还是一个蝌蚪……|嘿嘿……窝想次一大口，浪口气 biu 臭……|……不，窝还是算了。",
        "FarmHouse_Crib_NewbornSleeping": "{0} is sleeping. / {0}正在睡觉。",
        "NutHint_Squawk": "*Awk* / （叽叽喳喳）",
        "SummitBoulder": "It seems impossible to budge... / 好像完全挪不动……",
        "AnimalHouse_Incubator_Hatch_RegularEgg": "A new baby chick hatched! / 孵化出了一只小鸡！",
        "ManorHouse_MayorFridge_Initial": "It's the mayor's fridge. It's mostly full of milk and iced tea. / 这是镇长的冰箱。里面装满了牛奶和冰茶。",
        "Secret_Note_Name": "Secret Note / 秘密纸条",
        "ManorHouse_MayorFridge_ConsumeBeets": "You quickly place the beets in the fridge. Wait a sec... there's a note taped to the milk. It's addressed to you: / 你赶紧把甜菜放在冰箱中。等等……牛奶盒上贴了一张纸条。留言是给你的：",
        "Beach_Mariner_PlayerHasItem": "Old Mariner: Don't be shy, now. Show that amulet to the one you intend to marry. / 老水手：鼓起勇气来。把护身符送给你想结婚的另一半。",
        "FieldOfficeDonated_3": "To think... generations have come and gone while this little bone lay hidden beneath the soil. Now it's mine! / 你想想……几代人在这块土地上来了又走，而这根小小的骨头却始终藏在土里。而现在它是我的了！",
        "MineCart_Destination_Cancel": "Cancel / 取消",
        "Desert_Return_No": "Not yet / 再等等",
        "AnimalHouse_Incubator_Hatch_VoidEgg": "A new chick hatched... It looks odd. / 孵化出了一只鸡……样子有点奇怪。",
        "NutHint_Caldera": "Atop fire mountain... / 在火山顶上……",
        "LockedDoor_OpenRange": "It's locked... (Open {0} - {1}) / 上锁了……（营业时间：{0}~{1}）",
        "SeedShop_BuyBackpack_Question36": "Backpack Upgrade -- 36 slots / 背包升级：36格",
        "Theater_Poster_0": "Now Playing: \"{0}.\" / 正在上映：《{0}》。",
        "Saloon_Arcade_Minecart_Menu": "= Junimo Kart = / = 祝尼魔赛车 =",
        "Blacksmith_Clint_Shop": "Shop / 商店",
        "ScienceHouse_Carpenter_NotEnoughHardwood": "Sorry... You have the money, but I also need {0} pieces of hardwood. / 抱歉……你虽然有足够的钱，但我同时还需要 {0} 块硬木。",
        "CommunityCenter_AreaCompletion2": "This house was empty for years... The trees moved in and so did we. / 这个房子空置好多年了……树都在里面落地生根了，我们也一样。",
        "FarmHouse_SpouseAttacked6": "Get out! / 滚！",
        "BeachNightMarket_PainterClosed": "Famous Painter Lupini: Come back when the market opens, if you wish to purchase my fine work. / 著名画家卢皮尼：如果你想购买我的艺术品，请在市场开放时再来。",
        "IslandNorth_CaveHelp_3": "Over here! / 在这边！",
        "BoatTunnel_DonateIridiumHint": "The anchor could be repaired with 5 iridium bars. / 可以用 5 块铱锭修复船锚。",
        "Sewer_MagicSeal": "There's some kind of force-field blocking your path. / 有某种力场阻挡着你的去路。",
        "Caroline_Tea_Event2": "My mind is empty and free to wander... / 我的思绪空虚，随意徘徊……",
        "CommunityCenter_AreaName_FishTank": "Fish Tank / 鱼缸",
        "Saloon_Arcade_Cowboy_Continue": "Continue Journey / 继续旅程",
        "NutHint_BuriedArch": "Buried near bones... / 埋在骨头旁边……",
        "ArchaeologyHouse_Gunther_Donate": "Donate To Museum / 向博物馆捐赠",
        "ScienceHouse_Renovation_OpenBedroom": "Open Bedroom/Removes the wall separating your bedroom and the entrance room./Select an area for the renovation. / 开放卧室/拆除分隔卧室和门厅的墙。/选择装修区域。",
        "Railroad_Box_Initial": "It's an empty box. / 这是一个空箱子。",
        "AnimalShop_Marnie_Absent": "Closed for the day.\n\n-Marnie / 今天休息。\n\n——玛妮",
        "Gourmand_Finished": "*Kriibbitt*... Good to see you again, my friend.|You have my blessing to cultivate these fields. May the rains be with you! / 咯哩哩哩……李又来了，biu 滴朋友。|希望李还在种辣些 biu 大的果子，小子！",
        "Farm_GrandpaNote": "{0}-\n\nWait for my return on the dawn of your third year.\n\n-Grandpa / {0}：\n\n等你踏入第三年，我就会回来了。\n\n——爷爷",
        "WizardTower_WizardShrine": "           The Shrine Of Illusions\nMake an offering of 500g to change your appearance? / 是否花500金使用幻觉神龛改变你的外表？",
        "WitchHut_Goodbye": "Goodbye, {0}. / 再见，{0}。",
        "AdventureGuild_KillList_Serpent": "Serpents / 飞蛇",
        "MensLocker_WrongGender": "That's the men's locker room... you can't go in there! / 这是男更衣室……你不能进去！",
        "IslandSouth_ResortWillOpenSign": "The beach resort will be open tomorrow. / 海滩度假村明天将正常营业。",
        "Club_QiCoins_BuyStarter": "You have 0 Club Coins. Buy a starter pack for 1000g? / 您有 0 赌场硬币。是否花费 1,000 金购买新手包？",
        "Caroline_Sunroom_Door": "Caroline only lets her friends enter here... / 卡洛琳只允许她的朋友进入……",
        "IslandNorth_CaveHelp_1": "Anyone there? / 有人在吗？",
        "Journal_Name": "Journal Scrap / 日记残页",
        "BusStop_NotEnoughMoneyForTicket": "You don't have enough money. / 你身上的钱不够。",
        "Farm_1SlimeEscaped": "A slime escaped during the night. / 一个史莱姆在夜间逃跑了。",
        "IslandNorth_Event_SafariManAppear": "tropical_island_day_ambient/-1000 -100/farmer 20 48 1/skippable/pause 1000/viewport 21 47 true/pause 1000/playSound thudStep/addTemporaryActor SafariGuy 16 32 22 45 2 true ???/move SafariGuy 0 3 3/pause 1000/speak SafariGuy \"Thank you! I thought I was done for... $h#$b#I've been stuck in this cave for months!\"/pause 500/faceDirection SafariGuy 2/pause 300/showFrame SafariGuy 16/pause 600/emote SafariGuy 28/speak SafariGuy \"...One more cave mushroom salad and I would've gone off the deep end... *shudder* ...so rubbery...$s\"/pause 500/showFrame SafariGuy 0/pause 500/faceDirection SafariGuy 3/pause 500/translateName SafariGuy Strings\\NPCNames:ProfessorSnail/speak SafariGuy \"Anyway... I'm Professor Snail.#$b#I've been conducting a survey of this island's flora and fauna for the last year. Truly a remarkable place!\"/pause 400/faceDirection SafariGuy 2/pause 250/faceDirection SafariGuy 3/speak SafariGuy \"Well, I think I'll go back to my tent and freshen up a little. I'm afraid I smell like mushrooms...$s#$b#Hey... you should stop by the tent sometime! An enterprising individual like yourself could be a major asset in my projects... hee hee! Farewell.$h\"/pause 200/showFrame SafariGuy 17/pause 800/showFrame SafariGuy 12/pause 200/advancedMove SafariGuy true 1 0 0 4/pause 250/end position 20 48 / tropical_island_day_ambient/-1000 -100/farmer 20 48 1/skippable/pause 1000/viewport 21 47 true/pause 1000/playSound thudStep/addTemporaryActor SafariGuy 16 32 22 45 2 true ???/move SafariGuy 0 3 3/pause 1000/speak SafariGuy \"谢谢你！我以为我死定了……$h#$b#我被困在这个山洞里几个月了！\"/pause 500/faceDirection SafariGuy 2/pause 300/showFrame SafariGuy 16/pause 600/emote SafariGuy 28/speak SafariGuy \"要是再让我吃洞穴里的蘑菇沙拉我就得疯了……（打颤）……太难嚼了……$s\"/pause 500/showFrame SafariGuy 0/pause 500/faceDirection SafariGuy 3/pause 500/translateName SafariGuy Strings\\NPCNames:ProfessorSnail/speak SafariGuy \"是这样……我是蜗牛教授。#$b#去年我一直在调查这个岛上的动植物。这地方真的不得了！\"/pause 400/faceDirection SafariGuy 2/pause 250/faceDirection SafariGuy 3/speak SafariGuy \"嗯，我觉得我得先回帐篷收拾一下自己。我现在怕是闻起来跟蘑菇似的……$s#$b#嘿……你可以找个时间到帐篷来找我！像你这样有进取心的人可以成为我研究项目的主力人员……嘿嘿！再会。$h\"/pause 200/showFrame SafariGuy 17/pause 800/showFrame SafariGuy 12/pause 200/advancedMove SafariGuy true 1 0 0 4/pause 250/end position 20 48",
        "NutHint_VolcanoMining": "{0} nutty stone in fire mountain... / 还有 {0} 个在火山岩石里……",
        "MineCart_DestinationWithPrice": "{0} ({1}g) / {0}（{1} 金）",
        "AdventureGuild_KillList_LineFormat_None": "{0}/{1} ???? / {0}/{1} ????",
        "CommunityCenter_AreaName_BoilerRoom": "Boiler Room / 锅炉房",
        "BusStop_DesertOutOfService": "The bus to Calico Desert is out of service. / 通往卡利科沙漠的巴士已暂停营业。",
        "BoatTunnel_DonateBatteriesHint": "This machine could be repaired with 5 battery packs. / 可以用 5 个电池组修理这台机器。",
        "ScienceHouse_CarpenterMenu_Construct": "Construct Farm Buildings / 建造农场建筑",
        "Beach_Mariner_Player_Male": "lad / 小子",
        "Town_JojaSign_Destroyed": "Out of Business. / 歇业。",
        "ManorHouse_DivorceBook_CancelQuestion": "Cancel your divorce? / 是否取消离婚申请？",
        "IslandNorth_CaveTool_1": "It's too weak. / 这个太脆了。",
        "Club_CalicoJack_HS": "This table's for the big shots. It's a 1000 coin bet. / 这一桌是下大注的。每次下注是 1000 硬币。",
        "SeedShop_MoneyBox": "I'm taking the day off to visit the island. Please place your money in the box. No cheating! / 我今天放假去岛上玩。请把钱放进箱子里。不准白拿！^     -Pierre / ——皮埃尔",
        "Club_CalicoJack": "Wanna play some CalicoJack? This is the 100 coin table. / 想玩 21 点吗？这是 100 硬币赌注的赌桌。",
        "AdventureGuild_KillList_VoidSpirits": "Void Spirits / 虚空怪",
        "FieldOfficeDonated_0": "Ah... Now this is a truly fascinating piece of natural history! Thank you. / 啊……这块东西记录的自然历史真是令人着迷！谢谢你。",
        "ManorHouse_DivorceBook_NoSpouse": "Pelican Town Marriage Log... After marriage, you may file for divorce here. Let's hope that isn't necessary! / 鹈鹕镇婚事志……婚后，你可以在这里提交离婚申请。但愿你永远用不着此功能！",
        "IslandNorth_CaveTool_0": "That won't work. / 这个不管用。",
        "Theater_Poster_1": "\"{0}\" / 《{0}》",
        "CommunityCenter_AreaCompletion1": "We are the Junimos... Keepers of the forest. / 我们是祝尼魔……森林的守护者。",
        "FarmHouse_SpouseAttacked9": "Help! / 救命！",
        "FarmHouse_Bed_GoToSleep": "Go to sleep for the night? / 今晚要睡了吗？",
        "NutHint_Journal": "Hidden in the pages of the journal... / 藏在日记的某页……",
        "AdventureGuild_KillList_Mummies": "Mummies / 木乃伊",
        "BeachNightMarket_PainterSold": "Famous Painter Lupini: My apologies... I have no more paintings to sell today. / 著名画家卢皮尼：我很抱歉……我今天的画都卖光了。",
        "CommunityCenter_AreaName_CraftsRoom": "Crafts Room / 工艺室",
        "CommunityCenter_AreaCompletion4": "So many wonderful bundles... thank you! Thank you! / 这么多美妙的收集包……太感谢你了！谢谢！",
        "WitchHut_NoOffering": "You don't have the necessary offering. / 你并没有所需的祭品。",
        "Theater_Poster_Coming_Soon": "Coming soon: \"{0}.\" / 即将上映：《{0}》。",
        "CommunityCenter_AreaName_Vault": "Vault / 金库",
        "Town_SpecialCharmQuestion": "Driver: Hey kid... I need a lucky break... why don't 'cha bring me a 'rabbit's foot'? I'll make it worth your while. / 司机：嘿，小孩……我需要一点幸运的休息时间……为什么不带给我一只“兔子的脚”？我不会让你白花时间。",
        "Gourmand_RequestQuestion": "Ah... You have something to show me? / 小子，李在外面种辣个东西吗？",
        "Saloon_MoneyBox": "I'm tending the bar on Ginger Island today, but I won't let that stop you from buying something! / 我今天要在姜岛上的酒吧调酒，但你还是可以买东西的！^     -Gus / ——格斯",
        "FieldOfficeFinale": "distantBanjo/-1000 -1000/farmer 4 8 0/addCraftingRecipe Ostrich Incubator/addMailReceived fieldOfficeFinale/skippable/addTemporaryActor SafariGuy 16 32 3 8 0 true character/translateName SafariGuy Strings\\NPCNames:ProfessorSnail/pause 1000/viewport 4 6 true/pause 4000/speak SafariGuy \"Wow...#$b#Look how far we've come!$h\"/faceDirection SafariGuy 1/speak SafariGuy \"The collection looks fantastic, and it's all thanks to you, @.\"/emote farmer 32/speak SafariGuy \"Here, as a way of saying 'thanks', I want to teach you something.\"/faceDirection farmer 3/pause 700/playSound reward/message \"Learned how to craft 'Ostrich Incubator'\"/pause 400/speak SafariGuy \"This device will allow you to raise ostriches back home. Just place the incubator in a barn, place an ostrich egg inside, and wait...\"/faceDirection SafariGuy 0/speak SafariGuy \"Getting your hands on an ostrich egg is a different story, though... I'll leave that up to you!\"/pause 400/faceDirection farmer 0/pause 500/speak SafariGuy \"Heh... Well... now the real work begins.#$b#I'll be studying these bones for years to come!\"/faceDirection SafariGuy 1/faceDirection farmer 3/speak SafariGuy \"Farewell, @!\"/pause 600/end / distantBanjo/-1000 -1000/farmer 4 8 0/addCraftingRecipe Ostrich Incubator/addMailReceived fieldOfficeFinale/skippable/addTemporaryActor SafariGuy 16 32 3 8 0 true character/translateName SafariGuy Strings\\NPCNames:ProfessorSnail/pause 1000/viewport 4 6 true/pause 4000/speak SafariGuy \"哇……#$b#看看我们收集到了多少东西！$h\"/faceDirection SafariGuy 1/speak SafariGuy \"收集了这么多东西可太棒了，这都是你的功劳啊，@。\"/emote farmer 32/speak SafariGuy \"这样吧，作为感谢，我想教你一些东西。\"/faceDirection farmer 3/pause 700/playSound reward/message \"已学会制作“鸵鸟孵化器”。\"/pause 400/speak SafariGuy \"这个设备可以让你在家养鸵鸟。把孵化器放在畜棚里，放一个鸵鸟蛋进去，然后等待……\"/faceDirection SafariGuy 0/speak SafariGuy \"不过，怎么拿到鸵鸟蛋就是另一回事了……这事还得你自己来！\"/pause 400/faceDirection farmer 0/pause 500/speak SafariGuy \"哈哈……接下来真正的工作才刚要开始。#$b#我要用好几年的时间去研究这些骨头！\"/faceDirection SafariGuy 1/faceDirection farmer 3/speak SafariGuy \"有缘再会，@！\"/pause 600/end",
        "BeachNightMarket_Closed": "Opens at 5pm. / 下午 5 时开放。",
        "IslandFieldOffice_Survey_PurpleFlower_Question": "How many purple flowers can be found on the island? / 岛上可以找到多少朵紫色的花？",
        "BuyTicket": "Buy a ticket for {0}g? / 要花 {0} 金买票吗？",
        "FarmHouse_SpouseAttacked1": "What the...? / 怎么回事……？",
        "Farm_GreenhouseRuins": "Whatever this once was, it's now in ruins. / 不管这里曾经是什么，现在只留下了一片废墟。",
        "NutHint_MusselStone": "{0} stuck in shelly stones by shore... / 还有 {0} 个在岸边的贝壳里……",
        "Town_PickupTruck": "It's just the back of Lewis' old pickup truck... / 只不过是刘易斯的旧皮卡车的后车厢而已……",
        "FarmHouse_SpouseAttacked2": "Ahh!! / 啊！",
        "IslandNorth_CaveHelp_0": "Help! / 救命！",
        "ScienceHouse_Renovation_RemoveSouthernRoom": "Remove Southern Room/Removes the room to the south of your bedroom./Select an area for the renovation. / 移除南侧房间/移除卧室南侧的房间。/选择装修区域。",
        "IslandSouth_ResortWillCloseSign": "The beach resort will be closed tomorrow. / 海滩度假村明天将暂停营业。",
        "NutHint_SouthEastBuried": "{0} buried... Pirate's cove... / 还有 {0} 个埋在……海盗湾……",
        "SeedShop_BuyBackpack_Question24": "Backpack Upgrade -- 24 slots / 背包升级：24格",
        "ManorHouse_LedgerBook_Singleplayer": "Pelican Town Ledger Book... It looks like the mayor uses this to keep track of finances. / 鹈鹕镇账目表……看起来镇长是用这个来跟踪财务状况。",
        "NutHint_NorthHidden": "{0} hidden in the north... / 还有 {0} 个埋在北边……",
        "ManorHouse_LedgerBook_SharedWallets_CancelQuestion": "Cancel splitting up funds? / 要取消分配资金吗？",
        "MineCart_Destination_Mines": "Mines / 矿井",
        "JoshHouse_Alex_Trash": "There's a bunch of protein bar wrappers. / 一大堆蛋白棒的包装纸。",
        "Saloon_Arcade_Minecart_EndlessMode": "Endless Mode / 无尽模式",
        "Beach_FixBridge_Hint": "Hmmm... With 300 pieces of wood this could be fixed. / 唔……要是有 300 块木头就能把它修好。",
        "BusStop_NoDriver": "Please return when a bus driver is present. / 请等待司机出现后再回来乘车。",
        "ChallengeShrine_Activated": "Your request will be granted overnight. / 你的请求将在一夜之后得到批准。",
        "Club_ClubSeller": "Psst... I have a 'Statue of Endless Fortune' for sale... only 1,000,000g. What do you say? / 喂……我有一个“无尽财富之雕像”出售……看在跟你有缘的份上，只收你 1,000,000 金。你有兴趣吗？",
        "Tunnel_TunnelSafe_Initial": "It's a battery powered lock-box. Unfortunately, there's no battery in it. / 这是一个电池供电的保险箱。可惜的是，没上电池。",
        "Beach_Mariner_PlayerBuyItem_Question": "Old Mariner: Ah, I can see it in yer eyes... There be a special someone in yer heart. Just so happens I'm sellin' a 'Mermaid's Pendant'. Give that to yer intended and they'll know exactly what you mean. / 老水手：啊，从你的眼神看得出来你一定是爱上某人了。恰好我这里有出售“美人鱼吊坠”。你把它送给心上人，对方就明白你的意思了。",
        "AdventureGuild_KillList_DustSprites": "Dust Sprites / 灰尘精灵",
        "DoorUnlock_NotFriend_Couple": "You're not good enough friends with {0} or {1} to enter their bedroom. / 只有{0}或{1}的好朋友才能进入他们的卧室。",
        "Saloon_ColaMachine_Question": "Buy a Joja Cola for 75g? / 花费 75 金购买 Joja 可乐？",
        "Gourmand_Intro": "*Kribbibbit*... Who dares to enter my nest?|Ah... A humble farmer, come to cultivate my lands... How fortunate!|Oh, how the rains have blessed me! / 咯哩哩哩……是谁？李就是辣个在窝房子外面种地的农民吗，小子？",
        "Club_QiCoins": "You have {0} Club Coins. / 你有 {0} 赌场硬币。",
        "ManorHouse_LedgerBook_TransferCancel": "Cancel / 取消",
        "Mines_GoUp": "Go up one level / 进入上一层",
        "BoatTunnel_DonateHardwood": "Donate 200 hardwood for hull repairs? / 要捐赠 200 块硬木修复船体吗？",
        "Beach_GoneFishingMessage": "    Gone fishing.\n\n   I'll be back tomorrow. / 钓鱼去也。明日归。",
        "Farm_NSlimesEscaped": "{0} slimes escaped during the night. / {0} 个史莱姆在夜间逃跑了。",
        "FarmHouse_SpouseAttacked10": "Get your sword! / 拿出你的剑！",
        "FarmHouse_SpouseAttacked4": "Aiii! / 哎！",
        "Forest_HatMouseStore_Abandoned": "It looks abandoned... / 这里似乎早被遗弃了……",
        "Mines_Infested": "This area is infested... / 这个区域被入侵了……",
        "Club_CalicoJack_Play": "Play / 开始",
        "Gil_Telephone": "Hey. 150 Magma Sprites, huh? I'm impressed.#$b#Tell you what... I'm gonna give you Marlon's tellie-phone number. He don't like me givin' it out, but I think you've earned it.#$b#If you ever need to use the Item Recovery Service, but don't wanna run all the way out here... just give us a ring. Sound good? / 嗨。搞定了 150 只熔岩精灵？真是厉害。#$b#那么……我会给你马龙的电话号码，他不喜欢我把这个告诉别人，但我觉得这是你应得的。#$b#如果你需要使用物品恢复服务，但又不想跑到这里来……给我们打个电话就行了。听起来不错吧？",
        "CommunityCenter_AreaName_BulletinBoard": "Bulletin Board / 布告栏",
        "JojaMart_SignUp": "If you become a Joja Member, the community center will become a Joja Warehouse, and you will no longer be able to refurbish it. However, Joja will provide an alternative means to improving the town. Are you sure you want to join? / 当你成为 Joja 的一员后，社区中心就会变成 Joja 的仓库，而你将无法翻新它。不过，Joja 会通过其他方式发展镇子。你确定要加入吗？",
        "NutHint_Gourmand": "Kribbit... Gurrrp... / 咯哩哩……呼噜噜……",
        "ArchaeologyHouse_Gunther_Collect": "Collect Rewards / 收集奖励",
        "Club_CalicoJack_Rules1": "The objective is to get as close to 21 as possible. Cards range from 1 to 9, except for the first card which can be as high as 11. Each player starts with two cards, but the dealer's first card remains hidden. Each turn you can choose to draw a random number between 1 and 9 or pass. / 游戏的目的是尽可能接近 21 点。牌从 1 点至 9 点不等，除了第一张牌可能是高达11点以外。每个玩家一开始会获得两张牌，但庄家的第一张牌是隐藏牌。每回合你可选择抽一张 1 点到 9 点之间的随机牌，或者选择放弃该轮抽牌。",
        "MineCart_OutOfOrder": "Out of order / 已损坏",
        "HaleyHouse_SewingMachine": "It's a sewing machine... But I'm not sure how to use it. / 这是一台缝纫机……不过我不确定该怎么使用。",
        "Mines_FallenFar": "You fell {0} levels. Ouch! / 你掉了 {0} 层。痛！",
        "qiNutDoor": "You hear a strange voice from behind the door...#'Only the greatest walnut hunters may enter here.' / 你听到门后传来一个奇怪的声音……#“只有最强的核桃猎人才能进入。”^    Your current status: {0}/100 / ——你现在的进度：{0}/100",
        "BusStop_ReturnToHorse1": "{0} is wondering where you've been. / {0}正纳闷你去了哪里。",
        "Theater_MovieEnd": "The movie has concluded for tonight. We hope you enjoyed the show! / 今晚的电影已结束。希望你看得满意！",
        "LockedDoor": "It's locked... / 上锁了……",
        "IslandSecret_Event_BirdieIntro": "tropical_island_day_ambient/-1000 -1000/farmer 20 58 3/skippable/addTemporaryActor Birdie 32 32 17 58 3 true ???/animate Birdie false true 1000 8 9/pause 1000/viewport 18 58 clamp true/pause 1000/emote Birdie 8/pause 1000/speak Birdie \"Oh... a visitor?#$b#Come closer, child.\"/pause 400/move farmer -1 0 3/pause 300/emote Birdie 40/speak Birdie \"I haven't had a visitor in many moons...$s#$b#I almost forgot what other people looked like!\"/pause 1000/speak Birdie \"Well, I suppose now that you're here, I may as well ask you for a favor.\"/pause 500/textAboveHead Birdie \"Come...\"/pause 500/playFramesAhead 3/stopAnimation Birdie/extendSourceRect Birdie reset/warp Birdie 18 58/viewport move 1 0 2000/move Birdie 0 -1 2/move Birdie 2 0 1/move farmer 1 0 1/pause 500/speak Birdie \"Have you seen that wrecked ship on the south shore?#$b# My husband was the captain. A pirate, he was.#$b#He set sail one day, never to return. Took me three years sailing the high seas to find his remains.$s\"/emote Birdie 28/speak Birdie \"*sigh*...$s#$b#I've been here ever since, dear.$s#$b#...Guarding his bones...\"/faceDirection farmer 2 true/playSound batScreech/animate farmer false true 100 94/jump farmer/pause 1500/stopAnimation farmer/faceDirection farmer 0/faceDirection Birdie 2/speak Birdie \"My child... If I could only find a keepsake of his, it would bring me such peace.$s\"/pause 400/textAboveHead Birdie \"Wait here...\"/move Birdie -1 0 0/move Birdie 0 -1 3/warp Birdie -100 -100/playSound doorClose/faceDirection farmer 0/faceDirection Birdie 2/pause 1000/playSound Ship/pause 1000/playSound Ship/playSound crafting/pause 1000/playSound doorClose/warp Birdie 20 56/move Birdie 0 1 2/speak Birdie \"Here, take this. It's an old photograph that washed up on shore.#$b#It's all I have to offer... but somehow, I think it will help you find what I seek.\"/pause 500/unskippable/playSound coin/awardFestivalPrize memento true/pause 10/addQuest 130/pause 1700/end / tropical_island_day_ambient/-1000 -1000/farmer 20 58 3/skippable/addTemporaryActor Birdie 32 32 17 58 3 true ???/animate Birdie false true 1000 8 9/pause 1000/viewport 18 58 clamp true/pause 1000/emote Birdie 8/pause 1000/speak Birdie \"哦……有人来访？#$b#过来，孩子。\"/pause 400/move farmer -1 0 3/pause 300/emote Birdie 40/speak Birdie \"这儿已经好久没来过人了……$s#$b#我都快忘了别人长什么样了！\"/pause 1000/speak Birdie \"嗯，既然你都到这了，我不妨请你帮个忙。\"/pause 500/textAboveHead Birdie \"过来吧……\"/pause 500/playFramesAhead 3/stopAnimation Birdie/extendSourceRect Birdie reset/warp Birdie 18 58/viewport move 1 0 2000/move Birdie 0 -1 2/move Birdie 2 0 1/move farmer 1 0 1/pause 500/speak Birdie \"你看到南岸那艘沉船了吗？#$b#我丈夫是那艘船的船长，他曾是个海盗。#$b#有一天他启航后就再也没有回来。我在公海上航行了三年才找到他的遗体。$s\"/emote Birdie 28/speak Birdie \"唉……$s#$b#孩子，自那以后我就一直在这儿。$s#$b#……守卫他的遗骨。\"/faceDirection farmer 2 true/playSound batScreech/animate farmer false true 100 94/jump farmer/pause 1500/stopAnimation farmer/faceDirection farmer 0/faceDirection Birdie 2/speak Birdie \"孩子，如果我能找到他的纪念品，它将带给我莫大的安宁。$s\"/pause 400/textAboveHead Birdie \"稍等一下……\"/move Birdie -1 0 0/move Birdie 0 -1 3/warp Birdie -100 -100/playSound doorClose/faceDirection farmer 0/faceDirection Birdie 2/pause 1000/playSound Ship/pause 1000/playSound Ship/playSound crafting/pause 1000/playSound doorClose/warp Birdie 20 56/move Birdie 0 1 2/speak Birdie \"给你，拿上这个，这是一张被冲到岸上的旧照片。#$b#我能给你的只有这个了……不知道为什么，我就是觉得能帮助你找到我要的东西。\"/pause 500/unskippable/playSound coin/awardFestivalPrize memento true/pause 10/addQuest 130/pause 1700/end",
        "ManorHouse_DivorceBook_Cancelled": "Your divorce request has been cancelled. / 你的离婚申请已取消。",
        "FarmHouse_SpouseAttacked3": "#!*#%*! / #!*#%*!",
        "Mines_LeaveMine": "Leave the mine / 离开矿井",
        "BoatTunnel_DonateHardwoodHint": "The hull could be repaired with 200 pieces of hardwood. / 可以用 200 块硬木修复船体。",
        "ArchaeologyHouse_Rearrange": "Would you like to rearrange the museum's collection? / 你想重新排列博物馆的藏品吗？",
        "ManorHouse_LAF_FarmhandItems": "Retrieve items from offline farmhands / 获取离线农场主的物品",
        "SkullCave_SkullDoor_Unlock": "You insert the skull key into the keyhole. It's a perfect fit! / 你把头骨钥匙插入钥匙孔内。完美契合！",
        "BoatTunnel_willyText_random0": "Sorry if I smell like fish, heh! / 我是不是一股鱼腥味啊，哈哈！",
        "AdventureGuild_KillList_CaveInsects": "Cave Insects / 山洞昆虫",
        "Backwoods_MonsterGrave": "Abigail took a life to save mine...#I'll never forget that. / 阿比盖尔为了救我，夺走了一条生命……#我永远不会忘记此事。",
        "Mountain_AdventurersGuildNote": "      * Adventurer's Guild *\n\n    Proven adventurers only. /       * 冒险者公会 *\n \n    仅限货真价实的冒险者。",
        "ManorHouse_LedgerBook_MergeWallets": "Merge Funds / 合并资金",
        "NutHint_VolcanoLava": "Fire mountain... Hidden down fire river... / 火山……藏在火河下游……",
        "Beach_FixBridge_Question": "Use 300 pieces of wood to fix the bridge? / 是否消耗 300 块木头修桥？",
        "Sewer_DogStatueCancel": "None, I changed my mind... / 不，我改变了主意……",
        "Farm_WeedsDestruction": "The spreading weeds have caused damage to your farm. / 疯长的杂草危害了你的农场。",
        "ManorHouse_LedgerBook_Leave": "Leave / 离开",
        "ManorHouse_DivorceBook_Cancelled_Krobus": "You've changed your mind about kicking {0} out. / 你对踢走{0}一事回心转意了。",
        "Railroad_Box_ConsumeShell": "You throw the shell into the box. Immediately, a note falls down from the rafters above: / 你将贝壳扔入箱子。随即，一张纸条从上面的椽子落下：",
        "Farm_OtherPlayerMailbox": "That's not your mailbox. / 那不是你的邮箱。",
        "ScienceHouse_Carpenter_NotEnoughWood": "Sorry... You have the money, but I also need {0} pieces of wood. / 抱歉……你虽然有足够的钱，但我同时还需要 {0} 块木头。",
        "IslandFieldOffice_Survey_PurpleFlower_Correct": "Yes, yes... that seems very accurate. Thank you!$h / 对，没错……这个数字看起来非常准确。谢谢你！$h",
        "ManorHouse_LAF_DonationItems": "Collect lost items and incomplete deliveries / 获取遗失物品和未完成的订单物品",
        "BeachNightMarket_WarperQuestion": "Shrouded Figure: I can send you home for 250g. / 裹布人：只需 250 金，我就可以送你回家。",
        "Gourmand_Request_1_Success": "*Gurrrp*... Yes... This is it!|Heh... It reminds me of an old girlfriend... *gurp*...|Look here... I could tickle you with this!|...But, I won't. / 呼噜噜……不错。biu 长滴，跑过去的时候……biu 挠痒痒。|嘿嘿……浪窝想起了窝的前女友……（呼噜）……|嘿嘿……现在窝想给李挠痒痒……|……不，窝就算了。",
        "SeedShop_BuyBackpack_Response2000": "Purchase (2,000g) / 购买（2000 金）",
        "Mines_DoNothing": "Do nothing / 不进行任何操作",
        "ManorHouse_LedgerBook_SendMoney": "Send Money / 转账",
        "BeachNightMarket_GiftGiverQuestion": "Merchant: Hello there! Care for a cup of coffee? / 商人：你好！爱喝咖啡吗？",
        "IslandFieldOffice_Welcome_0": "Greetings! / 你好呀！",
        "CommunityCenter_JunimosReturned": "The Junimos have returned to the spirit world. / 祝尼魔已经回到灵界。",
        "Gourmand_RequestFailed": "*Kriibbitt*... What is the meaning of this?! You haven't grown the thing which I seek... Now go! / 咯哩哩哩……李没有种窝想要的辣个东西……种上兹后再来早窝……",
        "IceCreamStand_ComeBackLater": "Come back when someone's working. / 等有人工作时回来。",
        "Farm_GrandpaShrine_PlaceDiamond": "You place the diamond on Grandpa's Shrine. / 你将钻石放进爷爷的神龛。",
        "Theater_MovieEndReEntry": "The movie has concluded. / 电影已结束。",
        "WomensLocker_WrongGender": "That's the women's locker room... you can't go in there! / 这是女更衣室……你不能进去！",
        "ManorHouse_LedgerBook_SeparateWallets_TransferQuestion": "Who would you like to send money to? / 你想要给谁转账？",
        "AnimalShop_Marnie_Supplies": "Supplies Shop / 补给品商店",
        "Blacksmith_Clint_Geodes": "Process Geodes / 砸开晶石",
        "Mines_Overrun": "This area is overrun with monsters. / 这个区域被怪物占据了。",
        "IceCreamStand_NotSummer": "Closed until summer. / 夏季开放。",
        "NutHint_IslandFishing": "{0} deep in the water... / 还有 {0} 个在水的深处……",
        "AnimalHouse_Incubator_Hatch_DuckEgg": "A new baby duckling hatched! / 孵化出了一只小鸭！",
        "Submarine_Done": "Captain: We're back! Make sure not to leave any fish lying around. / 艇长：我们回家了！千万不要忘记拿鱼。",
        "IslandFieldOffice_Survey_Prompt_LeftPlant": "Island Survey -- Please report the number of purple flowers present on the island. / 岛屿调查：请报告岛上紫色花的数量。",
        "Club_ClubSeller_Yes": "I'll take it. / 买买买。",
        "ManorHouse_MayorFridge_MrQiNote": "'Good job, kid. Your final task: Give the sand dragon his last meal. -Mr. Qi' / “干得好，孩子。你的最后一个任务：给沙之巨龙最后一餐。——齐先生”",
        "IslandHut_Event_ParrotBoyIntro": "continue/-1000 -1000/farmer 7 7 3/skippable/specificTemporarySprite removeSprite 777/addTemporaryActor ParrotBoy 16 32 5 2 2 true ???/pause 2000/viewport 5 7 true/pause 2000/emote ParrotBoy 8/pause 1500/message \"The boy looks at you with curious eyes...\"/pause 1500/animate ParrotBoy false true 500 17 0/playSound parrot_squawk/pause 1000/playSound parrot_squawk/pause 800/stopAnimation ParrotBoy/specificTemporarySprite parrotHutSquawk/pause 800/move farmer -2 0 0/pause 500/emote farmer 8/pause 1000/message \"He seems to have a close bond with the parrots.\"/pause 500/message \"But he's too shy to approach you right now.\"/pause 1400/faceDirection farmer 1/pause 500/message \"Perhaps making friends with the parrots could earn his trust?\"/pause 1000/end position 5 7 / continue/-1000 -1000/farmer 7 7 3/skippable/specificTemporarySprite removeSprite 777/addTemporaryActor ParrotBoy 16 32 5 2 2 true ???/pause 2000/viewport 5 7 true/pause 2000/emote ParrotBoy 8/pause 1500/message \"男孩用好奇的眼神看着你……\"/pause 1500/animate ParrotBoy false true 500 17 0/playSound parrot_squawk/pause 1000/playSound parrot_squawk/pause 800/stopAnimation ParrotBoy/specificTemporarySprite parrotHutSquawk/pause 800/move farmer -2 0 0/pause 500/emote farmer 8/pause 1000/message \"他似乎与鹦鹉关系密切。\"/pause 500/message \"但他现在很怕生，不敢接近你。\"/pause 1400/faceDirection farmer 1/pause 500/message \"也许和鹦鹉交朋友可以赢得他的信任？\"/pause 1000/end position 5 7",
        "AdventureGuild_KillList_LineFormat_OverTarget": "{0} {2} * / {0} {2} *",
        "ChallengeShrine_AlreadyActive": "You've already put in a request. / 你已经提出了请求。",
        "NutHint_GoldenCoconut": "Inside hard, gold thing... / 藏在金色的、硬邦邦的里面……",
        "Saloon_Arcade_Minecart_Exit": "Exit / 退出",
        "ManorHouse_LedgerBook_CancelMerge": "Cancel Merging Funds / 取消合并资金",
        "SeedShop_Abigail_Drawers": "It's full of clothes... wait. There's a sword hidden under the clothes. / 里面放满了衣服……等等。衣服下面藏有一把剑。",
        "ScienceHouse_CarpenterMenu_RenovateCabin": "Make Cabin Renovations / 装修船舱",
        "FieldOfficeDonated_Reward": "And would you look at that! With this donation, we've got another full set piece completed.$h#$b#I've got a little something waiting for you behind the counter, when you're ready for it! / 看看！加上你拿过来的部位，我们又凑齐了一整套骨头。$h#$b#我在柜台后面给你准备了些小东西，你有空就来拿！",
        "NutHint_NorthBuried": "{0} buried in the north... / 还有 {0} 个埋在北边……",
        "ScienceHouse_Renovation_AddSouthernRoom": "Add Southern Room/Adds a room to the south of your bedroom./Select an area for the renovation. / 添加南侧房间/在卧室南侧添加一个房间。/选择装修区域。",
        "Tunnel_TunnelSafe_MrQiNote": "'Your first task: Bring a rainbow shell to the train platform. Leave it in the box. -Mr. Qi' / “你的第一个任务：带一个彩虹贝壳到火车站台。把贝壳放进箱子里。——齐先生”",
        "CommunityCenter_AreaName_AbandonedJojaMart": "Abandoned JojaMart / 废弃 Joja 超市",
        "CommunityCenter_AreaName_Pantry": "Pantry / 茶水间",
        "NutHint_IslandShrine": "Hidden shrine in rain forest... / 藏在雨林里的神庙……",
        "SeedShop_Yoba": "Altar of Yoba / 由巴祭坛",
        "BeachNightMarket_PainterQuestion": "Famous Painter Lupini: I'm selling this painting for 1200g. What do you say? / 著名画家卢皮尼：我的这幅画卖 1200。你觉得如何？",
        "ManorHouse_DivorceBook_Question": "File for divorce? There is a 50,000g fee. / 是否提出离婚申请？需要花费 50,000 金。",
        "AdventureGuild_KillList_Slimes": "Slimes / 史莱姆",
        "FarmHouse_SpouseAttacked5": "Die! / 去死！",
        "Beach_Mariner_PlayerNotUpgradedHouse": "Old Mariner: I can see that sparkle in yer eye, {0}. Ye must be head over heels in love. But I'm afraid a bigger house is essential for a happy marriage. / 老水手：从你的眼神我就能看得出你是坠入爱河了，{0}。但是想要保障幸福的婚姻，一所大房子是必须有的。",
        "SamHouse_Sam_Trash": "Looks like Sam cleans his trash bin regularly. / 看来山姆有定期清空垃圾桶的好习惯。",
        "ScienceHouse_Carpenter_UpgradeHouse3": "I can add a cellar to your house. The cellar can be used to age certain products, like wine and cheese. It will cost 100,000g. Are you interested? / 我可以替你的房子加盖一个地窖。地窖可用于保存葡萄酒和奶酪之类的产品。此升级需要消耗 100,000 金。你确定吗？",
        "ManorHouse_DivorceBook_CancelQuestion_Krobus": "Cancel your eviction? / 要取消你的驱逐令吗？",
        "Saloon_Arcade_Cowboy_NewGame": "Start New Journey / 开始新旅程",
        "AdventureGuild_KillList_Bats": "Bats / 蝙蝠",
        "Town_specialCharmNoFoot": "Driver: Come back when you got a 'rabbit's foot' on ya, kid. / 司机：你一搞到“兔子的脚”就回来，孩子。",
        "Gourmand_Request_0": "You must grow for me... that sweet delight, which is both pink and juicy...|Do not pluck it from the earth! I wish to see it in its natural state... / 李给窝种……辣个粉红色的东西……多兹的辣个……",
        "ManorHouse_DivorceBook_Question_Krobus": "Kick {0} out of your house? / 要把{0}踢出你家吗？",
        "IslandNorth_CaveHelp_2": "I'm stuck! / 我被困住了！",
        "Blacksmith_Clint_Leave": "Leave / 离开",
        "AdventureGuild_ItemRecovery": "Item Recovery Service / 物品恢复服务",
        "Forest_OpenedSewer": "You unlock the sewer hatch with the Rusty Key! / 你使用生锈的钥匙打开了下水道的井盖！",
        "WitchHut_EvilShrineCenterInactive": "-Dark Shrine of Memory- / ——记忆之黑暗神殿——^The statue stares through you... / 雕像的锐利眼神透视你的身体……",
        "IslandFieldOffice_Survey_Yes": "Ready to report / 已准备报告",
        "IslandSouth_ResortClosedWillOpenSign": "The beach resort will open back up tomorrow. Keep it closed? / 海滩度假村明天将恢复营业。要继续暂停营业吗？",
        "Gourmand_Request_0_Success": "*Gurrrp*... Yes... This is it!|...It's bringing me back to the old days... sunny days, when things were sweeter...|*slurp*... Oh, I could take a big, juicy bite...|...But, I won't. / 呼噜噜……就是辣个。biu 粉红色滴……biu 多兹的……|……浪窝回想起过去的时候啊……阳光很大，东西很甜……|（哧溜）……窝想要次一口 biu 多兹的……|……不，窝就算了。",
        "MineCart_Destination_Town": "Town / 城镇",
        "Club_ClubSeller_NotEnoughMoney": "Hey, I said 1,000,000g! This isn't gonna cut it. / 朋友，100 万金是跳楼价了！你这点钱不够啊。",
        "AdventureGuild_KillList_Footer": "\n  -See Gil to claim your rewards. / \n——找吉尔对话以获取任务奖励。",
        "AnimalHouse_Incubator_HouseFull": "An egg is ready to hatch, but the building is full. / 一只蛋已经准备好孵化了，但是建筑里已经没有空间了。",
        "WitchHut_EvilShrineRightDeActivate": "\n        -Dark Shrine of Night Terrors- / ——夜惊之黑暗神殿——^The ancient magi-seal of protection will be restored, preventing monsters from appearing on your farm at night.^Make an offering of one Strange Bun?\n       / 古老的魔法保护屏障会被恢复，防止怪物在夜间出没你的农场。^是否确定献祭一个奇怪小包子？",
        "DoorUnlock_NotFriend_Female": "You're not good enough friends with {0} to enter her bedroom. / 只有{0}的好朋友才能进入她的卧室。",
        "CommunityCenter_AreaCompletion5": "When we're done here, we'll return to the other world. / 等我们完成这里的任务之后，就会返回另一个世界。",
        "Gourmand_InProgress": "Ah... I see you are growing the thing I seek. However, it is still but a child. Come back when it has matured... / 啊……窝看到李种辣个东西了。但是现在还是咻~小。等长到 biu 大了再来吧……",
        "AdventureGuild_KillList_Skeletons": "Skeletons / 骷髅",
        "Desert_Trader_Closed": "Closed until the 18th for the Pelican Town night market. / 由于鹈鹕镇夜市，关门至 18 号。",
        "ScienceHouse_CarpenterMenu_UpgradeHouse": "Upgrade House / 升级房子",
        "NutHint_WestBuried": "{0} buried in the west... / 还有 {0} 个埋在东边……",
        "AdventureGuild_KillList_PepperRex": "Pepper Rex / 霸王喷火龙",
        "Club_CalicoJack_Rules2": "Once you pass, the dealer's hidden card is revealed. She must draw until her total reaches or exceeds 18. If either player exceeds 21 on their turn, they lose. If the dealer passes, then all cards are revealed and the highest score wins. / 一旦你放弃抽牌，庄家隐藏的牌会被亮出。庄家必须抽到总数等于或大于 18 点。如果任何一个玩家超过 21 点，那么他们就输了。如果庄家放弃抽牌，那么所有的牌都会被亮出，点数最高者获胜。",
        "ManorHouse_LAF_Check": "The town's 'Lost and Found' box. / 镇上的失物招领箱。",
        "ScienceHouse_CarpenterMenu_CommunityUpgrade": "Community Upgrade / 社区升级",
        "ManorHouse_DivorceBook_Filed_Krobus": "You've decided to kick {0} out of the house. If you change your mind, come back here before night's end. / 你已决定要把{0}踢出你家。要是你改变了主意，请在天亮前回来。",
        "ScienceHouse_Carpenter_UpgradeHouse2": "I can increase the size of your house and add a nursery. It will cost {0}g and you'll also need to provide me with {1} pieces of hardwood. Are you interested? / 我可以扩建你的房子并加盖一个婴儿室。此升级需要消耗 {0} 金和 {1} 块硬木。你确定吗？",
        "Gourmand_LastReward": "*Kriibbitt*... Yes... You have done me a great service. You've given an old toad one last trip down memory lane...|Here's one last reward for you, friend. / 咯哩哩哩……太好了……窝全都想起来了！|谢谢李唤醒窝这么多回忆。|最后给李一个好东西，小子。",
        "ScienceHouse_CarpenterMenu": "What can I do for you? / 有什么可以帮你的吗？",
        "Submarine_SubmergeQuestion": "Captain: Ahoy there! Want to take the deep-sea fishing tour? It'll cost ya 1,000g. / 艇长：你好啊！想参加深海垂钓之旅吗？只要 1000 金。",
        "Caroline_Tea_Event1": "When I'm alone with relaxing tea... / 当我独自一人喝茶休息时……",
        "ManorHouse_LedgerBook_SeparateWallets_HostQuestion": "It's the mayor's ledger book. What would you like to do? / 这里是镇长的账目表。你想要做什么？",
        "ScienceHouse_Renovation_RemoveCornerRoom": "Remove Corner Room/Removes the room in the northeast corner of the house./Select an area for the renovation. / 移除角落房间/移除房子东北角落的房间。/选择装修区域。",
        "ScienceHouse_MoneyBox": "I'm on the island today, but you can still buy something. It's an honor system! / 我今天在岛上，但你还是可以买东西的。这是一种诚信制度！^     -Robin / ——罗宾",
        "Beach_Mariner_Player_Female": "miss / 小姐",
        "IslandNorth_CaveTool_3": "Try something else. / 试试别的吧。",
        "IslandNorth_CaveTool_2": "Hmm... / 唔……",
        "Town_mgThiefMessage": "Shadow Guy: Eeeeep! You caught me! I'm sorry! Take it! Take it! It looked so valuable, I couldn't help myself... / 暗影人：哇啊啊啊啊！你抓住我了！对不起！收下吧！收下吧！这看起来很值钱，我没忍住……",
        "MineCart_ChooseDestination": "Choose destination: / 选择目的地：",
        "IslandFieldOffice_Survey_PurpleStarfish_Question": "How many purple starfish can be found on the island? / 岛上可以找到多少只紫色海星？",
        "Tunnel_TunnelSafe_ConsumeBattery": "It worked! The lock-box swings open. Inside, there's a note: / 成功了！保险箱打开了。里面有一张纸条：",
        "IslandFieldOffice_Welcome_1": "Hello! / 你好！",
        "ScienceHouse_Renovation_AddCornerRoom": "Add Corner Room/Adds a room in the northeast corner of the house./Select an area for the renovation. / 添加角落房间/在房子的东北角落添加一个房间。/选择装修区域。",
        "BusStop_ReturnToHorse2": "Your loyal horse waits patiently for your return. / 你忠实的爱驹在耐心等你回来。",
        "BoatTunnel_boatcomplete": "All materials have been found!#The boat will be repaired overnight. / 所有材料都找齐了！#今天晚上会修好这条船。",
        "SeedShop_LockedWed": "Closed on Wednesdays. / 周三打烊。",
        "NutHint_VolcanoBarrel": "{0} encased in fire mountain gadgets... / 还有 {0} 个装在火山的小工具里……",
        "Beach_Mariner_PlayerBuyItem_AnswerYes": "Buy (5000g) / 购买（5000 金）",
        "AnimalHouse_Incubator_Hatch_GoldenEgg": "A sparkling golden chick hatched! / 一只闪闪发光的金色小鸡孵化了！",
        "Sewer_DogStatueQuestion": "Which skill's professions would you like to change? / 你想改变哪种技能的职业？",
        "ManorHouse_DivorceBook_Filed": "Your divorce papers have been filed, but your spouse won't know until tomorrow morning. If you change your mind, come back here before night's end. / 你的离婚申请已经入档，但你的配偶要到明早才知道。要是你改变了主意，请在天亮前回来。",
        "ScienceHouse_RobinAbsent": "Sorry! Shop's closed for the day... I'm at Caroline's place for aerobics club.\n\n-Robin / 抱歉，本店今天休息……店主去了卡洛琳家参加有氧俱乐部的活动。\n\n——罗宾",
        "Saloon_Arcade_Cowboy_Menu": "= Journey Of The Prairie King = / = 草原之王之旅 =",
        "BoatTunnel_DonateIridium": "Donate 5 iridium bars to repair the anchor? / 要捐赠 5 块铱锭修复船锚吗？",
        "CommunityCenter_AreaCompletion3": "We're happy to help... It's not our house, after all. / 我们很乐意帮忙……毕竟这房子不属于我们。",
        "Caroline_Tea_Event3": "Who knows what might appear? / 谁知道会出现什么？",
        "Club_CalicoJack_Rules": "Rules / 规则",
        "DoorUnlock_NotFriend_Male": "You're not good enough friends with {0} to enter his bedroom. / 只有{0}的好朋友才能进入他的卧室。",
        "AdventureGuild_KillList_Header": "------------------------------\n\t\t\t --Monster Eradication Goals--\n             \"Help us keep the valley safe.\"\n------------------------------ / ------------------------------ \n--消灭怪物的目的--\n“守护星露谷的安全。”\n------------------------------",
        "Hint": "Hint / 提示",
        "Club_CalicoJack_NotEnoughCoins": "Hey, the betting's fixed at 100 coins. You don't have enough. Go buy some coins from the machine if you want to play. / 哎，固定投注是 100 个硬币。你没有足够的硬币。想玩的话请到机器那里购买硬币。",
        "Mines_ResetMine": "Reset your progress in the mine?\n(You'll be back at mine level 1). / 确定重设你的矿井进程？\n     （你会重回第一层）。",
        "LockedDoor_FriendsOnly": "It's locked... Only {0}'s friends can enter uninvited. / 上锁了……仅限{0}的朋友可以随意出入。",
        "Saloon_Arcade_Minecart_ProgressMode": "Progress Mode / 关卡模式",
        "WitchHut_EvilShrineRightActivate": "-Dark Shrine of Night Terrors- / ——夜惊之黑暗神殿——^The ancient magi-seal of protection will be lifted, allowing monsters to appear on your farm at night.^Make an offering of one Strange Bun? / 古老的魔法保护屏障会被撤走，怪物会在夜间出没你的农场。^是否确定献祭一个奇怪小包子？",
        "ChallengeShrine_AlreadyHard": "         --Shrine Of Challenge-- / ——挑战之神庙——^Summon an ancient magi-seal protection, returning the mines to their original state? / 要召唤古老的魔法封印，让矿井重回原样吗？",
        "Club_Buy100Coins": "Buy 100 Qi Coins for 1,000g? / 是否花费 1000 金购买 100 齐币？",
        "Saloon_Arcade_Minecart_Inactive": "There's a skull-shaped keyhole... / 有着骷髅形状的锁眼……",
        "NutHint_TigerSlime": "Stripey slimes to the west... / 西边的条纹史莱姆……",
        "FestivalDay_DoorLocked": "It's locked... / 上锁了……",
        "Desert_Return_Question": "Return to Stardew Valley? / 是否返回星露谷？",
        "Beach_Mariner_PlayerBuyItem_AnswerNo": "Not now... / 暂时没这个打算……",
        "NutHint_IslandFarming": "{0} grow on the farm to the west... / 还有 {0} 个长在西边的农场里……",
        "Club_Bouncer_TextAboveHead1": "Now I'm angry! / 我现在很生气！",
        "Sewer_DogStatueFinished": "*woof* *woof* (It's done... now go to sleep...) / *沃夫* *沃夫*（完成了……现在去睡觉……）",
        "Desert_Return_Yes": "Yes / 是",
        "AnimalShop_MoneyBox": "I'm visiting the island today. If you need to buy anything, just leave the money in this box! / 我今天要参观岛屿。如果你要买什么东西，把钱放进箱子里就好！^     -Marnie / ——玛妮",
        "Beach_Mariner_PlayerMarried": "Old Mariner: Glad the amulet worked out for ye, {0}. / 老水手：很高兴护身符对你有用，{0}。",
        "NutHint_VolcanoMonsters": "{0} taken by monsters in fire mountain... / 还有 {0} 个被火山的怪物霸占着……",
        "AdventureGuild_KillList_RockCrabs": "Rock Crabs / 岩石蟹",
        "Desert_SandDragon_ConsumeEssence": "You place the essence in the dragon's maw. Only then do you notice a note hidden in the eye socket: / 你将精华放在龙的大嘴中。此时你才看得见龙的眼窝中隐藏着一张纸条：",
        "Gourmand_RequestIntro": "*Gurrp*... You see... my fields once teemed with fresh fruit and vegetables...|But I have grown old, and without the vigor of youth, my fields have turned to worthless dust...|*sigh*... What I would give to feast my eyes upon that banquet of delights, once more...|That's where you come in. / 呼噜噜……辣个土地以前新鲜滴吃滴可多嘞……唉……要四棱再有辣么多吃滴就好了。",
        "Woods_Statue": "--Old Master Cannoli--\n...Still searching for the sweetest taste... / --老师傅香炸奶酪卷--\n……依旧寻求着最甜的味道……",
        "IslandFieldOffice_Survey_Prompt_RightPlant": "Island Survey -- Please report the number of purple starfish present on the island. / 岛屿调查：请报告岛上紫色海星的数量。",
        "Club_Bouncer_PlayerClubMember": "You may enter. / 你可以进入。",
        "BoatTunnel_DonateBatteries": "Donate 5 battery packs to repair the ticket machine? / 要捐赠 5 个电池组修理售票机吗？",
        "ScienceHouse_Renovation_BuildCrib": "Build Crib/Builds a crib in your home./Select a location for the crib. / 制作婴儿床/在家里制作婴儿床。/选择婴儿床放置的位置。",
        "Gourmand_Request_2": "I would like to see the zesty ground fruit, which maketh the breath stink... / 窝想要次辣个很刺激的地上的果子，会浪口气变臭的辣个……",
        "Club_CalicoJackHS_NotEnoughCoins": "You need at least 1000 coins to play here. / 你至少需要 1000 硬币才能在这里玩。",
        "IslandFieldOffice_Survey_PurpleFlower_Wrong": "Hmm... That number doesn't fit my models at all... Maybe you should give it another shot tomorrow.$s / 嗯……这个数字跟我的建模差太多了……要不你明天再试试吧。$s"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Strings/MovieConcessions",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "SourSlimes_Name": "Sour Slimes / 酸味史莱姆",
        "TrufflePopcorn_Name": "Truffle Popcorn / 松露爆米花",
        "Popcorn_Name": "Popcorn / 爆米花",
        "CottonCandy_Description": "A large pink cloud of spun sugar. / 一大块由拔丝糖组成的粉色云朵。",
        "IceCreamSandwich_Description": "Vanilla ice cream sandwiched between two chocolate cookies. / 在两块巧克力饼干间夹着香草冰淇淋。",
        "CottonCandy_Name": "Cotton Candy / 棉花糖",
        "CappuccinoMousseCake_Description": "A small chocolate cake glazed with a cappuccino mousse. / 涂有卡布奇诺慕斯的小块巧克力蛋糕。",
        "JojaCola_Name": "Joja Cola / Joja 可乐",
        "RockCandy_Name": "Rock Candy / 糖冰棍",
        "JojaCorn_Description": "Joja's patented corn food, slathered in plenty of \"b'utter sauce\". / Joja 公司拥有专利的玉米食品，涂有大量的黄油酱。",
        "ChocolatePopcorn_Description": "It's normal popcorn... but with a chocolate coating. / 就是普通的爆米花……但是有巧克力涂层。",
        "JojaCorn_Name": "JojaCorn / Joja 玉米",
        "Fries_Name": "Fries / 薯条",
        "JojaCola_Description": "An extra-large cup of Joja's flagship soda. / 一份超大杯的 Joja 招牌汽水。",
        "Jawbreaker_Description": "It's a big, hard candy that lasts the whole movie! / 这是一颗又大又硬的糖果，够你舔一整部电影的时间！",
        "Jawbreaker_Name": "Jawbreaker / 大糖球",
        "SalmonBurger_Name": "Salmon Burger / 鲑鱼汉堡",
        "KaleSmoothie_Description": "It's loaded with vitamins and fiber. / 它富含维生素和纤维。",
        "JasmineTea_Description": "Green tea flavored with aromatic jasmine flowers. / 用芳香的茉莉花调味的绿茶。",
        "CappuccinoMousseCake_Name": "Cappuccino Mousse Cake / 卡布奇诺慕斯蛋糕",
        "Popcorn_Description": "Popped kernels of corn, dusted lightly with salt and drizzled with butter. / 爆开的玉米粒，撒上少许盐，淋上黄油。",
        "HummusSnackPack_Name": "Hummus Snack Pack / 鹰嘴豆泥小吃包",
        "StardropSorbet_Description": "A single drop of stardrop essence transforms this sorbet into an extraordinary treat. / 一滴星之果实的精华让这冰糕有非凡的滋味。",
        "AppleSlices_Name": "Apple Slices / 苹果脆片",
        "SalmonBurger_Description": "A thick slab of salmon on a lightly toasted sesame seed bun. / 一块厚实的三文鱼放在一个轻微烘烤过的芝麻籽小圆面包上。",
        "ChocolatePopcorn_Name": "Chocolate Popcorn / 巧克力爆米花",
        "SourSlimes_Description": "Tiny gummy slimes of assorted colors. They're sprinkled with an extremely sour powder. / 小的颜色各异的史莱姆软糖。上面撒有一层非常酸的粉末。",
        "StarCookie_Description": "A star-shaped shortbread cookie with rainbow sprinkles. / 撒有彩虹糖针的星形酥脆饼干。",
        "Fries_Description": "Thin slices of potato, deep fried and then lightly salted. / 将切成薄片的土豆高温油炸，然后撒上少许盐。",
        "JasmineTea_Name": "Jasmine Tea / 茉莉花茶",
        "PersonalPizza_Description": "A pizza small enough to enjoy as a snack. / 小到可以当做甜点享用的披萨。",
        "BlackLicorice_Name": "Black Licorice / 黑甘草糖",
        "TrufflePopcorn_Description": "Heirloom popcorn sprinkled with truffle salt. / 传家宝手艺制作的爆米花撒上松露盐。",
        "SaltedPeanuts_Description": "A classic salty treat. / 经典的咸味零食。",
        "Nachos_Name": "Nachos / 芝士玉米片",
        "StardropSorbet_Name": "Stardrop Sorbet / 星之果实冰糕",
        "AppleSlices_Description": "Crunchy and sweet little slices. / 又脆又甜的薄片。",
        "PanzanellaSalad_Name": "Panzanella Salad / 意式面包沙拉",
        "PersonalPizza_Name": "Personal Pizza / 个人披萨",
        "RockCandy_Description": "Flavored sugar crystals attached to a convenient stick. / 香甜的糖晶体依附在一根简单的棍子上。",
        "Nachos_Description": "Gooey, spicy cheese on top of freshly fried tortilla chips. / 在新鲜的油炸玉米片上涂满黏黏的、辣辣的起司。",
        "PanzanellaSalad_Description": "A summer salad of bread and tomatoes. / 用面包和西红柿做的夏季沙拉。",
        "IceCreamSandwich_Name": "Ice Cream Sandwich / 冰淇淋三明治",
        "BlackLicorice_Description": "A chewy candy with an intense, pungent flavor. / 一种有强烈刺鼻味道的耐嚼糖果。",
        "HummusSnackPack_Description": "It's crunchy and healthy. / 它吃起来松脆又健康。",
        "KaleSmoothie_Name": "Kale Smoothie / 羽衣甘蓝汁",
        "StarCookie_Name": "Star Cookie / 星形饼干",
        "SaltedPeanuts_Name": "Salted Peanuts / 盐渍花生"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Strings/MovieReactions",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "Linus_spring_movie_1_BeforeMovie": "I feel out of place here... I hope I'm not bothering anyone.$s / 我在这里感觉格格不入……希望我没有打扰到任何人。$s",
        "Evelyn_like_BeforeMovie": "It's very kind of you to invite an old lady to the movies.$h / 你能邀请我这样的老太太去看电影真是太善良了。$h",
        "Elliott_love_AfterMovie": "I feel as if my spirit is charged... as if the energy of the film was transferred to me. Incredible! / 我觉得我的灵魂好像充了能……就好像是电影的能量转移到了我身上。不可思议！",
        "Alex_like_BeforeMovie": "Hey, I'm pretty excited to see a movie! I'm gonna need a snack, though... / 嘿，我很高兴能看电影！不过，我需要一点吃的……",
        "Penny_love_BeforeMovie": "Oooh, I've been dying to see this! / 哦哦，我一直渴望能看这个！",
        "Marnie_love_BeforeMovie": "I know I'm going to love this movie! It was really nice of you to invite me, @.$h / 我知道我会喜欢这部电影的！你能邀请我真是太好了，@。$h",
        "Sam_like_BeforeMovie": "Hey, thanks for inviting me, @... It's really great that we have a movie theater in town now. / 嘿，谢谢你邀请我，@……现在在镇里有一家电影院真是太好了。",
        "Lewis_spring_movie_1_AfterMovie": "Fantastic! They really made Stardew Valley look beautiful, didn't they? If only they had featured Pelican Town itself...$h / 棒极了！他们真的让星露谷看起来很漂亮，是不是？要是他们也把鹈鹕镇也加进来就好了……$h",
        "Pierre_like_BeforeMovie": "I'm usually working all the time, so it's really nice to do something like this. / 我通常一直在干活，所以做这样的事真的很不错。",
        "Shane_love_BeforeMovie": "Heh. I'm actually interested in seeing this one... / 嘿。我对这部还真挺有兴趣的……",
        "Lewis_spring_movie_1_BeforeMovie": "The governor himself recommended this movie to me! / 州长亲自向我推荐了这部电影！",
        "Shane_dislike_DuringMovie": "Shane's slumped over... / 谢恩瘫倒了……",
        "Leah_dislike_AfterMovie": "That was kind of lowbrow, wasn't it? / 这电影有点浅薄，是不？",
        "Evelyn_dislike_DuringMovie_2": "Evelyn is covering her eyes. / 艾芙琳捂住了眼睛。",
        "Linus_dislike_DuringMovie": "Linus is looking at the floor... / 莱纳斯正在看地板……",
        "Demetrius_winter_movie_0_BeforeMovie": "I read about this one in the paper... didn't seem like the thing for me. But I'll give it a shot. / 我在报纸上读到过这部……看起来不像我喜欢的类型。但我会试试。",
        "Caroline_summer_movie_0_BeforeMovie": "I've always loved movies about the wild west, so I'm really excited to see this! / 我一直很喜欢西部片，所以看这个我真的很兴奋！",
        "Elliott_like_AfterMovie": "Very interesting... I'll be pondering that one for a while. / 很有趣……我会好好思考一阵的。",
        "Lewis_like_AfterMovie": "Hah! That wasn't bad at all... I'd say this one's 'Mayor Approved'.$h / 哈！这一点都不糟糕啊……我觉得这个可以“镇长赞成”。$h",
        "Robin_love_AfterMovie": "I'm all fired up, now! That was great.$h / 我好兴奋！太好看了。$h",
        "Krobus_fall_movie_0_BeforeMovie": "Psst... Hey, it's me, Krobus. Could you recognize me?$8 / 嘘……嘿，是我，克罗布斯，你能认出我吗？$8#$b#If anyone approaches us, you do the talking, okay?$8 / 如果有人找上我们，你来跟他说话，好吗？$8",
        "Sandy_love_BeforeMovie": "I'm so happy to have an excuse to come to Pelican Town! / 我很高兴能找到借口来鹈鹕镇！",
        "Demetrius_like_BeforeMovie": "Even if a movie is bad, it's interesting to analyze. / 即使一部电影不好，分析一下也很有趣。",
        "Jodi_like_BeforeMovie": "I hope the seats are plush, I've been on my feet all day! / 我希望座位够软，我一整天都在干活！",
        "Jas_love_BeforeMovie": "I'm really happy to see a movie! / 我很高兴能去看电影！",
        "Wizard_*_AfterMovie": "You pulled me from my studies for *this*? / 你把我从我的研究中拉出来就是为了……这个？",
        "Clint_like_DuringMovie": "It's just... *hic*... Joja Cola.$h / 这只是……嗝……Joja 可乐。$h^*whispers*...If you're, um... tired... you can put your head on my... my shoulder. Heh... or not!$4 / （轻声）……如果你……累了……可以把你的头放在我的……我的肩膀上。嘿……随便你！$4",
        "Jodi_love_BeforeMovie": "I saw this movie once, a long time ago. It's very romantic! / 很久以前我看过这部电影。太浪漫了！",
        "Emily_spring_movie_1_AfterMovie": "I feel a little bit smarter than I was before... don't you? / 我感觉比以前聪明了一点……你觉得呢？",
        "Shane_love_DuringMovie_2": "Shane's trying not to smile. / 谢恩在努力板着脸。 ",
        "Shane_summer_movie_0_DuringMovie": "I'm rooting for the villain... *urp* / 我支持那个反派……嗝",
        "Krobus_fall_movie_0_DuringMovie": "Not all shadow people are like that!$8 / 不是所有的影子人都是那样的！$8",
        "Abigail_summer_movie_0_AfterMovie": "Well the acting was awful, but I still had a great time.$h / 唔，表演很糟糕，但我还是看得很开心。$h",
        "Harvey_love_AfterMovie": "That was outstanding! I'm really glad that you brought me out for this, @.$h / 太出色了！我真的很高兴你带我来看，@。$h",
        "Jas_horror_DuringMovie": "I'm scared...$s / 我害怕……$s",
        "Clint_winter_movie_1_AfterMovie": "That movie was depressing...$s / 那部电影很令人沮丧……$s",
        "Abigail_spring_movie_1_DuringMovie": "I didn't know that! / 我之前都不知道这个！",
        "Sam_like_AfterMovie": "That wasn't bad! I might have to take Vincent to see this. / 不错！我可能得带文森特来看这个。",
        "Haley_dislike_BeforeMovie": "Oh, is this one of those 'fantasy' movies?$7 / 哦，这是不是那种“奇幻”电影？$7",
        "Maru_summer_movie_1_BeforeMovie": "It's a sci-fi movie, right? One of the things I like about sci-fi is seeing all the weird technologies they come up with. / 这是一部科幻电影，对吧？我喜欢科幻小说的一点就是能看到他们想出的各种奇怪技术。",
        "Abigail_summer_movie_0_BeforeMovie": "I can't believe they made a Prairie King movie... I hope it's good! / 真不敢相信他们拍了一部草原之王的电影……我希望它拍得够好！",
        "Caroline_love_DuringMovie": "I hope the poor little guy will be okay...$s / 我希望这个可怜的小家伙会没事……$s",
        "Penny_family_BeforeMovie": "Oh, '{0}'! This looks wholesome and fun! / 哦，《{0}》！看起来健康又有趣！",
        "Wizard_fall_movie_0_DuringMovie": "And to think... the layman has no idea that this is all raw, real footage! / 仔细想想……这外行人根本不知道这都是原本的、真实的镜头！",
        "Evelyn_like_AfterMovie": "I'm glad they're still making decent movies... I had a lot of fun! / 很高兴他们还在拍像样的电影……我看的很开心！",
        "Lewis_summer_movie_0_DuringMovie_2": "Mayor Lewis seems deep in thought... / 刘易斯镇长似乎在沉思……",
        "Robin_love_BeforeMovie": "I've been feeling kind of dull lately, so an action-packed movie is exactly what I need. / 我最近感觉有点闷，所以一部动感十足的电影正是我需要的。",
        "Sebastian_dislike_AfterMovie": "It's probably a fine movie for the target audience, but it's just not for me. / 对于那些目标观众来说，这也许是一部好电影，但不适合我。",
        "Leah_dislike_BeforeMovie": "From the movie poster, this one looks pretty cheesy. / 从电影海报上看，这部电影好像挺俗的。",
        "Gus_fall_movie_0_AfterMovie": "What was the point of that one? I don't get it. Maybe I'm too old.$s / 那有什么意义？我不明白。也许我太老了。$s",
        "Pierre_love_BeforeMovie": "I grew up watching old sci-fi flicks, so I'm interested to see a modern take on the genre. / 我从小就看那些旧的科幻电影，所以我对看一个现代的演绎版很有兴趣。",
        "Krobus_*_AfterMovie": "So, your species enjoys staring at flickering lights for hours on end? Very interesting...$8 / 所以，你们这种生物喜欢连续盯着闪烁的灯光看几个小时？真有趣……$8",
        "Dwarf_love_BeforeMovie": "Oh, wow! A palace constructed for the sole purpose of entertainment! / 哇！专为娱乐而建造的宫殿！",
        "Lewis_dislike_BeforeMovie": "Hmm... I guess it will be interesting to see what the young people are watching these days... / 唔……我想看看这些年轻人现在看什么会很有趣……",
        "Evelyn_love_BeforeMovie": "Before this theater came to town, I hadn't seen a movie in twenty years!$h / 要不是这个影院来我们镇，我都要超过二十年没看过电影了！$h",
        "Sebastian_like_BeforeMovie": "*shrugs*... The movie poster looked pretty cool, so I'm in. / （耸肩）……电影海报看起来很酷，所以我同意。",
        "Linus_spring_movie_1_DuringMovie": "Linus is looking at the floor... / 莱纳斯正在看地板……",
        "Alex_love_AfterMovie": "That was great! My legs are still tingling with the excitement. / 真的好看！我的腿还在兴奋地打颤。",
        "Sebastian_dislike_BeforeMovie": "I hope it's short... / 我希望电影不要太长……",
        "Maru_summer_movie_1_AfterMovie": "Well, I've never seen anything like *that* through my telescope... but it was really great!$h / 我从来没有从望远镜里看到过【那样的东西】……但这真的很棒！$h",
        "George_dislike_BeforeMovie": "Hmph... I'll take a nap during this one. / 唔……看这个的时候我要打个盹。",
        "Kent_dislike_BeforeMovie": "I'm not sure about this movie... / 我不确定这部电影要不要看……",
        "Harvey_dislike_DuringMovie_2": "Harvey's blood pressure is skyrocketing! / 哈维的血压在飞涨！",
        "Robin_like_AfterMovie": "That was a lot of fun, @. I'm glad we did this. / 电影很有意思，@。我很高兴我们能一起来。",
        "Harvey_dislike_DuringMovie": "I feel faint...$8 / 我感觉头晕……$8",
        "Wizard_fall_movie_0_DuringMovie_2": "There's a twinkle in Wizard's eye... / 巫师的眼睛里闪烁着光芒……",
        "Penny_spring_movie_0_BeforeMovie": "I'm looking forward to this! Jas and Vincent have been talking about it non-stop. / 我很期待！贾斯和文森特一直在不停地谈论这件事。",
        "Gus_summer_movie_1_AfterMovie": "As an amateur connoisseur, the weird obsession with gluten-based food was hilarious.$h / 作为一名业余鉴赏家，我觉得对面食的怪异痴迷很搞笑。$h",
        "George_dislike_AfterMovie": "Shameful! The trash they pass for 'movies' these days...  / 真是可怜！他们现在都是把什么垃圾当成“电影”的啊……",
        "Penny_spring_movie_0_DuringMovie": "Wow, it must be really hard leaving his family like that...$s / 哇，离开家人真的很难过……$s",
        "Abigail_spring_movie_1_AfterMovie": "That was really interesting. I liked the raccoons the best... they're so cute!$h / 这真的很有意思。我最喜欢那些浣熊……它们真可爱！$h",
        "Jas_horror_BeforeMovie": "I... I'm not sure I'm allowed to see this...$s / 我……我家里人大概不让我看这个……$s",
        "Leo_love_AfterMovie": "Did you see that? They showed the fern islands... that's where I'm from!$h / 你看到了吗？他们拍到了芬群岛……我就是从那儿来的！$h",
        "Leo_love_DuringMovie": "Leo is glued to the screen! / 雷欧被银幕深深吸引了！",
        "Vincent_dislike_BeforeMovie": "B... But... This movie is for grown-ups, isn't it?$s / 但……但……这部电影是给大人看的，不是吗？$s",
        "Maru_like_BeforeMovie": "I really like going to the theater, even if the movie's bad!$h / 我真的很喜欢去电影院，即使电影不好看！$h",
        "Sam_dislike_DuringMovie_2": "Sam is playing his handheld video game system. / 山姆正在玩他的掌机。",
        "Pam_*_AfterMovie": "Heh, that wasn't too bad! / 嘿，那还不算太差！",
        "Elliott_dislike_BeforeMovie": "It would be a lie to say I'm looking forward to this one...$s / 要说我很期待这部电影那我自己都不信……$s",
        "Lewis_dislike_AfterMovie": "Huh... I wonder if the messages in this movie are good for our community? / 嗯……我好奇这部电影中的信息是否对我们的社区有好处？",
        "Harvey_love_DuringMovie": "It really makes you think, doesn't it? / 这真的引人深思，是不是？",
        "Demetrius_spring_movie_1_AfterMovie": "Well, they definitely embellished some things, but it was still mostly correct! Anyway, I had a good time. / 嗯，他们肯定夸大了一些东西，但大体上还是正确的！不管怎样，我看得很开心。",
        "Alex_like_AfterMovie": "Hey, that was pretty good. Thanks for inviting me to this, @. / 嘿，电影挺好看的。谢谢你邀请我，@。",
        "Sebastian_love_BeforeMovie": "Hey. I heard this movie is pretty grim... I'm looking forward to it.$h / 嘿。我听说这部电影挺沉重的……我很期待。$h",
        "Elliott_like_BeforeMovie": "I've avoided all information about this film... I like to go in completely 'blind'! / 我有意避开了所有关于这部电影的信息……我喜欢完全“盲看”！",
        "George_love_AfterMovie": "Heh! That was actually pretty good! Thanks for inviting me. / 嘿！这电影真的相当不错！谢谢你邀请我。",
        "Caroline_love_BeforeMovie": "This movie looks so cute, I was really hoping someone would invite me! / 这部电影看起来真可爱，我一直希望有人邀请我！",
        "Maru_spring_movie_1_AfterMovie": "That was really interesting! I had no idea that so much life could be found in the big city. / 真有意思！我不知道大城市原来这么有活力。",
        "Penny_like_AfterMovie": "That was great! Thanks for seeing this with me! / 太棒了！谢谢你和我一起看这个！",
        "Caroline_dislike_BeforeMovie": "I have a feeling this one's going to be a let-down... But I'm still interested to give it a try. / 我总感觉这会令人失望的……但我还是有兴趣试一试。",
        "Marnie_like_BeforeMovie": "I'm pretty easy-going when it comes to movies... I like just about everything! / 在电影这方面我很随意的……我什么都喜欢！",
        "Jas_love_DuringMovie": "Jas is ecstatic! / 贾斯非常高兴！",
        "Linus_spring_movie_1_AfterMovie": "Why stare at a screen when you could experience these things yourself?$s / 当你自己能体验这些东西时，为什么要看别人做呢？$s",
        "Abigail_like_BeforeMovie": "Hey! Thanks for inviting me, I love going to the movies.$h / 嘿！谢谢你邀请我，我喜欢看电影。$h",
        "Kent_like_DuringMovie": "This is great... it reminds me of simpler times...$h / 这真是太棒了……它让我想起那单纯的时光……$h",
        "Dwarf_love_DuringMovie": "Dwarf seems to be in a deep trance... / 矮人似乎完全入迷了……",
        "Leah_love_AfterMovie": "That was great! The narrative was very loose, but I think it was intended to speak to the emotions, not the intellect. / 太棒了！叙事很松散，但我认为这部电影的目的是表达情感，而不是智慧。",
        "Penny_seen_like_BeforeMovie": "I saw this with {2}, it was pretty good! / 我已经和{2}看过了，相当不错！",
        "Gus_like_AfterMovie": "Not bad at all. I'm really glad I came! / 一点也不糟糕。我真的很高兴我来了！",
        "Penny_*_BeforeMovie": "Watching a movie with mom sure brings me back! / 和妈妈一起看电影肯定能让我恢复！",
        "Sam_summer_movie_1_AfterMovie": "*psst*... Don't tell anyone, but I wear the same type of socks as Wumbus. / 嘘……不要告诉别人，我穿的袜子和温布斯一样。",
        "Alex_summer_movie_1_AfterMovie": "Hah! I really liked it. But I dunno if I could survive on gluten pucks like that. / 哈！我真挺喜欢这片子！不过我不知道如果我像那样光吃面饼能不能活下来。",
        "Haley_like_AfterMovie": "That last scene... what did they mean by that? / 最后一幕……那是什么意思？",
        "Dwarf_love_AfterMovie": "I didn't understand a thing, but the flashing lights were mesmerizing! / 我什么也没看懂，但闪烁的灯光令我着迷！",
        "Penny_*_DuringMovie": "(Pam and Penny are watching intently!) / （帕姆和佩妮正全神贯注地看着！）",
        "Shane_dislike_AfterMovie": "I feel depressed...$s / 我感到很沮丧……$s",
        "Sam_summer_movie_1_DuringMovie_2": "Sam can't contain his laughter! / 山姆控制不了自己的笑声！",
        "Demetrius_spring_movie_1_BeforeMovie": "This one's right up my alley... you know I'm gonna love this.$h / 这个正是我的菜……你知道我会喜欢的。$h",
        "Leah_like_BeforeMovie": "I'm not sure what to expect with this movie, but I'm going to keep an open mind! / 我不知道这部电影会有什么，但我会避免抱有什么成见！",
        "Abigail_like_AfterMovie": "That was interesting... I wonder what I would've done in the same situation? / 很有趣……我很好奇如果碰到同样的情况，我会怎么做？",
        "Jas_horror_DuringMovie_2": "Jas is trembling. / 贾斯在颤抖。",
        "Haley_dislike_AfterMovie": "*yawn*... What? Oh... what was that movie about, again?$7 / （呵欠）……什么？哦……这部电影是关于什么的来着？$7",
        "Gus_summer_movie_1_BeforeMovie": "I saw a commercial for this on the TV. It looks really funny! / 我在电视上看到过它的广告。看起来真有趣！",
        "Sandy_love_AfterMovie": "That was a lot of fun, thanks for inviting me! I'd better head home soon... / 真的很有趣，谢谢你邀请我！我最好还是马上回家……",
        "Wizard_fall_movie_0_BeforeMovie": "I sense an arcane power permeating this building tonight... / 今晚我感觉到这座建筑里弥漫着一种神秘的力量……",
        "Abigail_love_BeforeMovie": "I love horror movies... I hope it's scary!$h / 我喜欢恐怖电影……希望这片子能拍得很可怕！$h",
        "Demetrius_winter_movie_1_BeforeMovie": "A short jaunt in the snow really gets the blood flowing. / 在雪地里游荡真能促进血液流动呢。",
        "Clint_like_BeforeMovie": "I guess it's 'guys night', huh? Does that mean I have to buy my own snacks? / 我猜是“男生之夜”吧？是不是说我必须自己买零食？^Oh... A... Are we on a date, then?$4 / 哦……那么，我们是在约会吗？$4",
        "Evelyn_dislike_BeforeMovie": "I've never been a fan of scary movies, but I'll try to keep an open mind. / 我对恐怖电影从不感冒，但我会尽量让自己不抱成见。",
        "Leah_spring_movie_1_AfterMovie": "That was great. I'm pretty sure I even saw my cabin in one of those Stardew Valley aerial shots!$h / 太好看了。我敢肯定我在那些星露谷航拍镜头里有看到我的小屋！$h",
        "Robin_like_BeforeMovie": "I'm not sure what this movie's about, but I don't really care! It's just good to get out of the house. / 我不确定这部电影是关于什么的，但我不在乎！出门逛逛就很好了。",
        "Maru_spring_movie_1_DuringMovie_2": "Maru's taking notes! / 玛鲁在记笔记！",
        "Abigail_love_DuringMovie_2": "Abigail is giggling! / 阿比盖尔在笑！",
        "Clint_winter_movie_1_DuringMovie_2": "Clint is scowling. / 克林特皱着眉头。",
        "Penny_spring_movie_0_DuringMovie_2": "Penny seems to be holding back some tears... / 潘妮似乎在忍着眼泪……",
        "Jas_horror_AfterMovie": "*sniff*...$s / （吸鼻子）……$s",
        "Sam_dislike_BeforeMovie": "It's an old movie with lots of talking, right? Hmm... $s / 这是一部有很多对话的老电影，对吧？唔……$s",
        "Gus_winter_movie_0_AfterMovie": "That was heartwarming... and somehow they make that fabled fruit seem so delicious. I'd love to taste it one day. / 真令人心动……不知何故，他们让传说中的水果看起来如此美味。我希望有一天能尝尝。",
        "Leah_spring_movie_1_BeforeMovie": "I've heard there's some really beautiful nature footage in this one... I'm really looking forward to it!$h / 我听说电影里有一些非常美的大自然镜头……我真的很期待！$h",
        "Evelyn_dislike_DuringMovie": "Is it over yet?$s / 结束了吗？$s",
        "Emily_love_AfterMovie": "That movie felt very spiritual, in a way... don't you agree? I loved it!$h / 那部电影感觉很有精神力……你同意吗？我很喜欢！$h",
        "Gus_fall_movie_0_BeforeMovie": "They say this movie is 'unconventional'... does that mean it's bad?$s / 他们说这部电影“不落俗套”……意思是不是说它不好？$s",
        "Sebastian_love_AfterMovie": "Best movie I've seen in a while... I wonder how they did some of those special effects?$h / 这是我最近看过的最好的电影……我想知道他们是怎么做出这些特效的？$h",
        "Emily_dislike_DuringMovie_2": "Emily is whispering to herself... / 艾米莉在低声自言自语……",
        "Penny_dislike_AfterMovie": "Sorry if I ruined the movie for you, it just wasn't really my favorite... / 如果我毁了你的电影，对不起，它真的不是我喜欢的……",
        "Emily_like_AfterMovie": "I feel positive after that one... that means it was a good movie!$h / 在那之后我感觉很不错……也就是说这是一部好电影！$h",
        "Evelyn_dislike_AfterMovie": "I had to close my eyes during most of it...$s / 我不得不大半场电影都闭着眼睛……$s",
        "Sam_horror_AfterMovie": "That was pretty good! I'm usually not scared by movies, but that one got to me a little... I don't think I'll take Vincent to see this. / 这很好看！我通常不害怕电影，但这部有点吓到我了……我想我不会带文森特来看这个。",
        "Clint_winter_movie_1_BeforeMovie": "This movie's supposed to be a romance, right? *sigh*$s / 这部电影应该是一部爱情片，对吧？唉……$s",
        "Jodi_love_AfterMovie": "That was lovely... The theme of the movie really resonated with me. Thanks for bringing me! / 那真可爱……这部电影的主题真的引起了我的共鸣。谢谢你带我来！",
        "Penny_horror_DuringMovie": "I can't look...$s / 我不敢看……$s",
        "Penny_dislike_DuringMovie": "... / ……",
        "George_love_BeforeMovie": "The newspaper gave this one '5 stars', so I'm willing to give it a go. / 报纸给这部评了“五星”，所以我愿意试试看。",
        "Alex_love_BeforeMovie": "I've been wanting to see this one for a while. Thanks for the ticket, @! / 我最近一直想看这个。谢谢你的票，@！",
        "Sam_summer_movie_1_DuringMovie": "This movie's hilarious! How do they come up with this stuff?$h / 这部电影很搞笑！他们是怎么想出这种东西的？$h",
        "Wizard_*_BeforeMovie": "... / ……",
        "Evelyn_love_AfterMovie": "I loved it... now you know why '{0}' is considered a classic. / 真好看……现在你该知道为什么《{2}》算是经典了吧。",
        "Vincent_dislike_DuringMovie": "Vincent is fidgeting in his seat. / 文森特在他的座位上烦躁不安。",
        "Abigail_love_DuringMovie": "Haha! It's not scary, but I love it.$h / 哈哈！并不可怕，但我喜欢。$h",
        "Jas_like_AfterMovie": "I thought it was good! It had... um... good 'die-a-log'! ...right? / 我觉得很好看！这电影……呃……“对、化”很不错！……我没说错吧？",
        "Abigail_dislike_BeforeMovie": "From seeing the trailer, this one looks like a real snoozefest...$6 / 从预告片来看，这部真的适合打盹……$6",
        "Willy_like_BeforeMovie": "Hehe... I'd never turn down a free movie! / 嘿嘿……我从不拒绝免费电影！",
        "Harvey_spring_movie_1_BeforeMovie": "I'm nervous about this one... *gulp* / 我看这个很紧张……（咽口水）",
        "Alex_summer_movie_1_BeforeMovie": "This one's supposed to be pretty funny, I'm looking forward to it. / 这片子应该挺好玩的，我很期待。",
        "Penny_family_AfterMovie": "I should totally bring the kids to see this sometime! / 我完全应该带孩子们去看这个！",
        "Caroline_dislike_AfterMovie": "That was silly... I bet Pierre would like it.$s / 太傻了……我敢打赌皮埃尔会喜欢的。$s",
        "Jodi_like_AfterMovie": "I'm not much of a movie buff... but I had a good time! Thanks, @. / 我不太喜欢电影……但我看得很愉快！谢谢，@。",
        "Abigail_dislike_AfterMovie": "*yawn*... that was pretty boring, wasn't it?$6 / （呵欠）……太无聊了，是不是？$6",
        "Marnie_like_AfterMovie": "I had a great time, @! Thanks for thinking of me. / 我看得很开心，@！谢谢你能想起我。",
        "Harvey_love_BeforeMovie": "I read a glowing review of this movie in the Zuzu City Times... / 我在《祖祖城时报》上读到过这部电影的好评……",
        "Penny_like_BeforeMovie": "Hey, I've heard some good things about this one! / 嘿，我听说这部评价很好！",
        "Demetrius_summer_movie_1_AfterMovie": "Great movie... but I wonder if there really is life beyond this planet? / 很棒的电影……但我很好奇这个星球上之外是否真的有生命？",
        "Penny_*_AfterMovie": "It's great to be able to do things as a family again! / 能再次一家人一起做事真是太好了！",
        "Leo_like_AfterMovie": "Wow... it was like magic! / 哇……感觉像是魔法一样！",
        "Harvey_dislike_BeforeMovie": "This movie seems a little intense for me...$s / 这部电影对我来说似乎有点激烈……$s",
        "Penny_dislike_BeforeMovie": "I can't say I would've picked this one myself, but I'll try to keep an open mind... / 我不敢说我自己看电影会选这个，但我会尽量让自己不抱成见……",
        "Elliott_love_BeforeMovie": "I foresee this to be an exquisite night! / 我已经预料今晚肯定很美妙！",
        "Krobus_fall_movie_0_AfterMovie": "I'm not used to wearing clothes... It's very uncomfortable!$8 / 我不习惯穿衣服……这很不舒服！$8",
        "Shane_love_AfterMovie": "When you're watching a good movie, you can forget about everything else... That's a gift. / 当你看一部好电影时，会把所有其他东西都抛在脑后……这是天赋。",
        "Linus_dislike_AfterMovie": "I'm not used to that much stimulation... sorry if I was a disappointing guest, @. I still appreciate your inviting me! / 我不习惯那么多的刺激……如果我让你失望了，@，对不起。我还是感谢你邀请我！",
        "Harvey_dislike_AfterMovie": "My body feels inflamed after that movie...$s / 看了这电影后，我感觉身体都红肿了……$s",
        "Alex_dislike_BeforeMovie": "This movie seems kind of nerdy, but I'll give it a shot. / 这部电影看起来略无聊，不过我还是试一试吧。",
        "Krobus_fall_movie_0_DuringMovie_2": "Krobus is stewing... / 克罗布斯坐立不安……",
        "Abigail_love_AfterMovie": "That was pretty campy, but I liked it.$h / 比较装腔作势，但我喜欢。$h",
        "Shane_like_BeforeMovie": "Buh... Yeah, I guess this might be okay. *sniff* *sniff* ... a snack might help. / 但……嗯，我觉得这应该还行。(嗅)(嗅)……有吃的就好了。",
        "Vincent_love_AfterMovie": "That was so fun! I wanna go see it again!$h / 太有趣了！我想再看一遍！$h",
        "Pierre_love_AfterMovie": "Hah! It wasn't what I expected, but I ended up really liking it! I really identified with Wumbus.$h / 哈！这跟我期待的不太一样，但我还是很喜欢！我真的很认同温布斯。$h",
        "Emily_dislike_DuringMovie": "Yoba, please protect me from the dark energy of this movie.$7 / 由巴，请保护我免受这部电影的黑暗能量的影响。$7",
        "Penny_comedy_AfterMovie": "Whew, I've got a cramp from all that laughing...! / 呼，我笑抽筋了……！",
        "Leo_like_DuringMovie": "Leo seems very interested in the movie. / 雷欧似乎对电影很感兴趣。",
        "George_like_BeforeMovie": "Hmph... Theaters aren't like they used to be... But the picture might be good enough. / 唔……影院跟以前不太一样了啊……不过电影应该相当好。",
        "Penny_seen_dislike_BeforeMovie": "Hmm, I think {2} took me to see this... / 唔，我想{2}已经带我去看过这个了……",
        "Kent_like_DuringMovie_2": "Kent has a rare smile on his face. / 肯特脸上露出了难得的微笑。",
        "Haley_winter_movie_0_BeforeMovie": "Mmm... It's nice and warm in here. Winter is my favorite time to go to the movies.$h / 嗯……这里很好、很暖和。冬天是我最喜欢的看电影的时候。$h",
        "Sebastian_like_AfterMovie": "It wasn't the best ever, but I had a pretty good time... thanks for inviting me. / 这不是最好看的，但我过得很愉快……谢谢你邀请我。",
        "Emily_like_BeforeMovie": "I'm happy to see a movie with you! I tend to get totally lost in the screen. / 我很高兴和你一起看电影！我总会完全迷失在屏幕中。",
        "Demetrius_winter_movie_1_DuringMovie_2": "Demetrius is furrowing his brow. / 德米特里厄斯皱起眉头。",
        "Caroline_love_AfterMovie": "That was adorable. Thanks so much for inviting me to this! / 真可爱。非常感谢邀请我来！",
        "Penny_comedy_DuringMovie": "Did they just...?! Hahahaha! / 他们刚刚是不是……？！哈哈哈哈！",
        "Maru_spring_movie_1_BeforeMovie": "Hey, @! I'm looking forward to this one... I hope we learn a lot!$h / 你好啊，@！我很期待这部……我希望我们能学到很多东西！$h",
        "Shane_like_AfterMovie": "Okay, I'll admit... I thought it was pretty good. / 好吧，我承认……我觉得很不错。",
        "Penny_seen_love_BeforeMovie": "Ooh, '{0}'! I saw this one with {2}! / 哦，《{0}》！我已经和{2}看过这个了！",
        "Emily_spring_movie_1_BeforeMovie": "I ate a handful of nuts to prepare for this movie... brain food! / 为了准备看这部电影，我还吃了一把坚果……那可是健脑食品！",
        "Pierre_like_AfterMovie": "Not bad! I wonder if they have any merchandise I could stock... / 不错！我想知道他们是否有我可以收藏的周边产品……",
        "Abigail_dislike_DuringMovie": "Wake me up if anything interesting happens.$6 / 如果发生有趣的事情，把我叫醒。$6",
        "Emily_dislike_AfterMovie": "My energy levels are low after that one...$3 / 看完之后我的能量水平就很低……$3",
        "Demetrius_spring_movie_1_DuringMovie": "Technically, that's not correct...$3 / 从技术上讲，这是不对的……$3",
        "Wizard_fall_movie_0_AfterMovie": "For those aware of the esoteric mysteries, that had deep significance... / 对于那些意识到这艰深的奥秘的人来说，它有着深远的意义……",
        "Krobus_*_BeforeMovie": "*ahem*... Hello! I am very excited to be at the visual entertainment center and to consume the popped corn... just like you!$8 / 咳……你好！我非常高兴能够来视觉娱乐中心然后吃爆开的玉米……就像你一样！$8#$b#*whisper*... how am I doing?$8 / （耳语）……我怎么样？$8",
        "Lewis_summer_movie_0_AfterMovie": "Heh, that was great! Really brought me back...$h / 嘿，这太好看了！真的把我带回到了过去……$h",
        "Clint_like_DuringMovie_2": "Clint is taking sips from an unmarked flask. / 克林特从没有标签的烧瓶中吸了一口。",
        "Clint_like_AfterMovie": "Hey... that was kind of fun... right?$h / 嘿……挺有意思的……是吧？$h",
        "Shane_summer_movie_0_AfterMovie": "Okay, I'll admit... I thought it was pretty good. / 好吧，我承认……我觉得很不错。",
        "Harvey_spring_movie_1_DuringMovie": "I'm scared!$8 / 我很害怕！$8",
        "Gus_like_BeforeMovie": "*sniff* *sniff* ... I smell something delicious... / (嗅)(嗅)……我闻到了好吃的东西……",
        "Shane_dislike_BeforeMovie": "Ugh... this is going to be painful. / 嗯……大概会很痛苦。",
        "Elliott_dislike_AfterMovie": "That was very mundane, don't you think? / 这片子很平庸，你不觉得吗？",
        "Jas_like_DuringMovie": "Jas is nodding and glancing sideways. / 贾斯在四处张望。",
        "Vincent_love_DuringMovie": "Vincent is having a blast! / 文森特玩得很开心！",
        "Kent_dislike_DuringMovie": "Kent is breaking out into a cold sweat... / 肯特出了一身冷汗……",
        "Emily_love_BeforeMovie": "When I saw the movie poster for this one, I felt a very positive sensation in the top of my head.$h / 当我看到这部电影的海报时，我莫名地产生了一种很不错的感觉。$h",
        "Sebastian_love_DuringMovie_2": "Sebastian has a grin on his face. / 塞巴斯蒂安脸上露出了笑容。 ",
        "Leah_love_BeforeMovie": "I'm really intrigued by this movie... I'm a sucker for the mysterious. / 我对这部电影很感兴趣……我对神秘事件无法抗拒。",
        "Caroline_summer_movie_0_AfterMovie": "That was great! It really felt authentic, with the costumes and everything. / 太棒了！感觉很真实，服装和其他部分都是。",
        "Kent_like_AfterMovie": "That was fun. When you're engrossed in a movie, all your cares and worries disappear. / 这很有趣。当你全神贯注于一部电影时，你所有的忧虑和烦恼都会消失。",
        "Haley_winter_movie_1_BeforeMovie": "Mmm... It's nice and warm in here. Winter is my favorite time to go to the movies.$h / 嗯……这里很好、很暖和。冬天是我最喜欢的看电影的时候。$h",
        "Sebastian_love_DuringMovie": "This cinematography is next-level. / 这电影的摄影一流。",
        "Demetrius_winter_movie_0_AfterMovie": "Nonsense! That was totally unscientific!$4 / 胡扯！这完全是不科学的！$4",
        "Alex_dislike_AfterMovie": "I can't tell if that was boring, or if I'm just not smart enough to understand it...$s / 我不知道是电影太无聊，还是我太笨了没法理解……$s",
        "Linus_dislike_BeforeMovie": "I feel out of place here... I hope I'm not bothering anyone.$s / 我在这里感觉格格不入……希望我没有打扰任何人。$s",
        "Emily_dislike_BeforeMovie": "I usually go to more positive movies, so this will be interesting. / 我通常看比较积极向上的电影，这部应该有点意思。",
        "Leo_love_BeforeMovie": "I'm excited to see this one... I want to learn everything about the world! / 我很期待这部电影……我想了解世界上的一切！",
        "Penny_horror_BeforeMovie": "I'm a little nervous... I don't usually watch scary movies.$s / 我有点紧张……我一般不看恐怖电影。$s",
        "Haley_winter_movie_1_AfterMovie": "That was very romantic. / 这真浪漫。",
        "Abigail_summer_movie_0_DuringMovie": "Listen... it's got that old familiar music.$h / 听……是那熟悉的老音乐。$h",
        "Harvey_like_BeforeMovie": "I don't watch a lot of movies, but this one's been well-received, right? / 我不常看电影，但是这个评价很不错，是吧？",
        "Penny_family_DuringMovie": "(Penny is smiling) / （潘妮在微笑）",
        "Demetrius_winter_movie_1_DuringMovie": "Longings of the heart...? Oh! You mean 'elevated levels of oxytocin in the limbic system'. / 心灵的渴望……？哦！你是说“边缘系统中催产素水平升高”吧。",
        "Jas_love_AfterMovie": "That was so much fun! Thanks for bringing me!$h / 太有趣了！谢谢你带我来！$h",
        "Penny_comedy_BeforeMovie": "I'm excited, I'm in the mood for a good laugh! / 我很兴奋，我真的想大笑一场！",
        "Jas_like_BeforeMovie": "This is a grown-up movie, right? I'll be okay! / 这电影是给成年人看的，对吧？我不要紧的！",
        "Harvey_spring_movie_1_DuringMovie_2": "Harvey is shaking! / 哈维在颤抖！",
        "Marnie_love_AfterMovie": "Oh, I'm so glad the family was alright in the end. And the cows, too!$h / 哦，我很高兴全家人最后都没事了。还有奶牛也是！$h",
        "George_like_AfterMovie": "Heh. Compared to most movies these days, it wasn't bad.$h / 嘿。跟现在的大多数电影相比，这还不赖。$h",
        "Sam_dislike_DuringMovie": "Huh? Oh! Yeah... The movie's... interesting...$10 / 嗯？哦！对……电影……挺有趣……$10",
        "Haley_winter_movie_0_AfterMovie": "I'm glad there was a good ending! / 有个好结局我很高兴！",
        "Pam_*_BeforeMovie": "Hey, kid. Thanks for inviting me. / 嘿，孩子。谢谢你邀请我。",
        "Clint_winter_movie_1_DuringMovie": "Why would she like THAT guy? Totally unrealistic if you ask me...$3 / 她为什么喜欢那个家伙？要我说这完全不现实……$3",
        "Vincent_love_BeforeMovie": "I'm so excited! My mom said I can have candy, too!$h / 我太激动了！妈妈说我也可以吃糖果！$h",
        "Leah_like_AfterMovie": "That was simple, but good... It's like the comfort food of cinema. / 故事挺简单的，但很好看……就像电影院里吃了很治愈的菜一样。",
        "Maru_like_AfterMovie": "That was an interesting choice, for the final scene. What do you think they meant by that? / 最后一幕这样拍是挺有趣的选择。你觉得那是什么意思？",
        "Caroline_like_AfterMovie": "That wasn't bad! I'll have to ask Abigail about it when I'm home, I'm sure she's seen it.$h / 不错！我回家后得问问阿比盖尔，她肯定看过了。$h",
        "Willy_like_AfterMovie": "Ah, that reminds me of a story me ol' Pops used to tell... / 啊，这让我想起了老波普斯经常讲的一个故事……",
        "Demetrius_winter_movie_1_AfterMovie": "The art of film has come a long way since those times, hasn't it? / 电影艺术从那个时代开始走过了很漫长的道路，是吧？",
        "Kent_like_BeforeMovie": "Thanks for inviting me to the movies, @. It's not easy to adjust back into the civilian lifestyle, but you've helped me feel really welcome. / 谢谢你邀请我去看电影，@。适应平民的生活方式并不容易，但你帮助我感受到了真正的欢迎。",
        "Maru_spring_movie_1_DuringMovie": "Ah, I see... that's very interesting! / 我明白了……很有趣！",
        "Haley_like_BeforeMovie": "Everyone's talking about this movie, so I've been wanting to see it. / 大家都在谈论这部电影，所以我一直想看。",
        "Lewis_like_BeforeMovie": "As mayor, I need to know what kinds of movies are being shown in our community. We have the tender minds of the next generation to worry about! / 作为镇长，我需要知道我们的社区里在放什么样的电影。我们要关心下一代的幼小心灵！",
        "Penny_love_AfterMovie": "Amazing! I hope they make another one! / 真棒！希望他们再出一部！",
        "Caroline_like_BeforeMovie": "'{0}'... I have no idea what this is about! I hope it's not violent. / 《{0}》……我不知道这到底是什么！我希望它不是暴力主题。",
        "Demetrius_like_AfterMovie": "Hmm... I wonder what aspect of human motivation is satisfied by the narrative of this film?$3 / 嗯……我想知道这部影片的叙事满足了人类动机的哪些方面？$3",
        "Lewis_summer_movie_0_DuringMovie": "(I wonder what kind of moustache wax he uses?) / （我很好奇他用什么样的胡子蜡？）",
        "Demetrius_spring_movie_1_DuringMovie_2": "Demetrius is scratching his chin... / 德米特里厄斯抓着他的下巴……",
        "Sam_dislike_AfterMovie": "Yeah... Uh... That one character was interesting... And, um... heh...$10 / 是的……呃……那个角色很有趣……还有……呃……$10",
        "Penny_horror_AfterMovie": "I hope I don't have nightmares tonight!$s / 希望我今晚不要做噩梦！$s",
        "Sam_summer_movie_1_BeforeMovie": "Oh man, I'm so excited for this! I heard it has a great soundtrack. / 哦天哪，我太激动了！我听说它的配乐很棒。",
        "Harvey_spring_movie_1_AfterMovie": "I have a fear of heights, so those soaring aerial shots really got to me... Still, I had a good time overall.$h / 我恐高，所以那些空中飞翔的镜头真的让我害怕……不过，总体来说，我看得挺愉快。$h",
        "Shane_love_DuringMovie": "Okay, this is good...$h / 不错，很好看……$h",
        "Abigail_spring_movie_1_BeforeMovie": "I'm excited to 'explore our vibrant world'... aren't you?$h / 我很高兴能《探索我们充满活力的世界》……你呢？$h",
        "Leo_like_BeforeMovie": "I'm really happy to be here. This is all so interesting! / 我真的很高兴能来到这里。一切都太有趣了！",
        "Shane_summer_movie_0_BeforeMovie": "Buh... Yeah, I guess this might be okay. *sniff* *sniff* ... a snack might help. / 但……嗯，我觉得这应该还行。(嗅)(嗅)……有吃的就好了。",
        "Gus_winter_movie_0_BeforeMovie": "It doesn't feel like the holidays until you've seen '{0}'! / 你看了《{0}》，才会有放假的感觉！",
        "Sam_horror_BeforeMovie": "So you like scary movies, huh? I'm a little surprised! / 你喜欢恐怖电影吗？我有点惊讶！",
        "Harvey_like_AfterMovie": "That was interesting! I'm going to be thinking about {0} one for a while. / 太有趣了！我会仔细思考{0}一段时间的。",
        "Penny_spring_movie_0_AfterMovie": "Thanks for taking me to this, I can't wait to tell the kids how good it was! / 谢谢你带我看这个，我迫不及待想告诉孩子们它有多好！",
        "Vincent_dislike_AfterMovie": "That was boring... I didn't understand anything.$s / 很无聊……我什么都看不懂。$s",
        "Demetrius_summer_movie_1_BeforeMovie": "This movie supposedly takes place in a 'futuristic' society... it will be interesting to see what that looks like! / 这部电影据说发生在一“未来”的社会……能看看那是什么样子肯定很有趣！",
        "Lewis_summer_movie_0_BeforeMovie": "I watched cowboy movies when I was a kid... I'm glad to see the art is still alive! / 我小时候就经常看牛仔电影……我很高兴看到艺术还有活力！",
        "Kent_dislike_AfterMovie": "That was challenging for me. Still, I appreciate you inviting me to this. / 这对我来说很有挑战性。不过，我很感谢你邀请我来看。"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Strings/Movies",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "Wumbus_Scene3": "His faithful servant, FoodBot, provides a steady stream of fried gluten pucks and 'red sauce'. / 他忠实的仆人，食品机器人，向他提供源源不断的油炸面饼和“红酱”。",
        "JourneyOfThePrairieKing_Title": "Journey Of The Prairie King: The Motion Picture / 草原之王之旅：大电影",
        "ZuzuCityExpress_Scene6": "The movie explores a timeless theme... the conflict between reason and emotion. / 这部电影探索了一个永恒的主题……理性与情感的冲突。",
        "ItHowlsInTheRain_Scene2": "'The following footage was salvaged from an abandoned camcorder 30 miles south of Grampleton' / “以下镜头是从格兰普立顿以南 30 英里处的废弃摄像机中抢救出来的。”",
        "BraveLittleSapling_Scene1": "The Brave Little Sapling / 勇敢的小树苗",
        "MiracleAtColdstarRanch_Scene1": "'The Miracle at Coldstar Ranch' / 《冷星牧场的奇迹》",
        "MiracleAtColdstarRanch_Title": "The Miracle At Coldstar Ranch / 冷星牧场的奇迹",
        "JourneyOfThePrairieKing_Scene1": "'Journey Of The Prairie King: The Motion Picture' / 《草原之王之旅：大电影》",
        "ItHowlsInTheRain_Scene4": "'(Heavy Breathing)... Look!' / （沉重的喘息）“……看！”",
        "NaturalWonders_Scene4": "Now we move north to the bustle of Zuzu City. It's a world of concrete and steel, illuminated by the glow of city light. / 现在我们往北走，来到繁华的祖祖城。它是一个由混凝土和钢铁组成的世界，有城市的光芒照亮。",
        "ZuzuCityExpress_Scene1": "'The Zuzu City Express' / 《祖祖城特快列车》",
        "ItHowlsInTheRain_Description": "A group of youngsters set out to discover the source of a mysterious sound. (Parental Supervision Required) / 一群年轻人开始寻找一个神秘声音的来源。（未成年人请家长陪同观看）",
        "NaturalWonders_Scene9": "The temperate climate of the valley is the perfect home for a variety of woodland creatures and insects. What a beautiful place! / 山谷的温带气候是各种森林生物和昆虫的完美家园。多美的地方啊！",
        "MiracleAtColdstarRanch_Scene3": "The Coldstar family is stranded... getting to town is impossible. Fortunately, the cows have enough hay to get by. / 冷星家族陷入困境……去不了城里。幸运的是，奶牛有足够的干草可以过活。",
        "ItHowlsInTheRain_Scene5": "(The camera lurches forward into the forest) / （摄像机摇晃着向前进入森林）",
        "ItHowlsInTheRain_Scene3": "'Did you hear that? I think it came from those woods... Let's go...' / “你听到了吗？我想它是从那些树林里传来的……我们走……”",
        "ZuzuCityExpress_Scene7": "Will she follow the directions of her rational mind, or the longings of her heart? / 她会追随自身理性思维的方向，还是她内心的渴望？",
        "Wumbus_Description": "An absurd sci-fi comedy centered around the life and times of a lumpy guy from another star. / 一部荒诞的科幻喜剧，以另一个星球上某个笨蛋的生活和时代为中心展开。",
        "Mysterium_Scene1": "'Mysterium' / 《神秘事迹》",
        "MiracleAtColdstarRanch_Scene12": "The next day, Mama Coldstar is astonished to find the tree adorned with cosmic fruit. / 第二天，冷星妈妈惊讶地发现树上零星点缀着宇宙果实。",
        "JourneyOfThePrairieKing_Scene7": "Thinking quickly, he fires a shot. / 思绪如电，他开了一枪。",
        "JourneyOfThePrairieKing_Scene11": "The End. / 谢幕。",
        "Wumbus_Title": "Wumbus / 温布斯",
        "JourneyOfThePrairieKing_Scene8": "But what's this? Water's flying everywhere! / 但发生了什么？水花四处飞溅！",
        "Wumbus_Scene5": "'Pshhaw!' / “啐！”",
        "ZuzuCityExpress_Scene3": "A young lady peers wistfully out the window. / 一位年轻的女士若有所思地凝视着窗外。",
        "ZuzuCityExpress_Description": "A beloved movie classic, carefully restored for modern theaters. / 一部备受喜爱的经典电影，经过精心重置，适合现代影院。",
        "BraveLittleSapling_Scene2": "The brave little sapling is leaving his home. He hesitates for a moment and turns around, knowing he won't be back for a long time... / 勇敢的小树苗正离开他的家。他犹豫了一会儿，转过身去，知道自己会离开很长一段时间……",
        "BraveLittleSapling_Scene4": "Oh no! Out of nowhere, it starts raining...! The little sapling goes into a sprint as thunderclouds loom overhead... / 哦不！突如其来开始下雨了……！乌云密布头顶，小树苗开始加速冲刺……",
        "Wumbus_Scene7": "Many scenes attempt to find humor in the absurdity of the modern lifestyle. / 许多场景试图在现代生活方式的荒谬中找到幽默。",
        "MiracleAtColdstarRanch_Description": "Against all odds, a family keeps the spirit of the Winter Star alive... / 尽管困难重重，一个家庭还是保持着冬星精神的延续……",
        "ItHowlsInTheRain_Scene9": "(Muffled cries and a strange shuffling sound can be heard) / （能听到低沉的叫声和奇怪的脚步声）",
        "ZuzuCityExpress_Scene8": "The movie ends before we ever find out... / 在我们找到答案之前，电影就结束了……",
        "MiracleAtColdstarRanch_Scene9": "In spite of their hunger, the family decorates the tree, keeping the promise of the Winter Star alive. / 尽管他们很饿，家里还是将这棵树装饰起来，让冬星的诺言永存。",
        "JourneyOfThePrairieKing_Scene9": "He's done it again! The thick mud stops the avalanche in its tracks. / 他又开了一枪！厚厚的泥土阻止了山崩。",
        "NaturalWonders_Scene6": "Far to the west, alone in the vast Gem Sea, lies Prairie Island. In spite of its name, this land is home to a diverse array of natural biomes. / 在遥远的西部，广阔的宝石海上，草原岛孤立其中。从它的名字可以看出，这片土地是各种各样的自然生物群落的家园。",
        "BraveLittleSapling_Scene8": "Farewell, little buddy! / 再见了，小家伙！",
        "NaturalWonders_Scene5": "The conditions may be harsh, but still, we find abundant life... / 这里的自然环境可能很恶劣，但我们仍然发现了大量的自然生命……",
        "MiracleAtColdstarRanch_Scene7": "Still, Papa Coldstar braves the treacherous conditions to cut down the winter star tree... / 尽管如此，冷星爸爸还是勇敢地冒着险恶的条件砍下了冬星树……",
        "ItHowlsInTheRain_Scene1": "It Howls In The Rain  / 它在雨中嚎叫",
        "ItHowlsInTheRain_Scene6": "'Oh, it's just you, Gary... *pant* *pant*... Stop grabbing my arm!' / “哦，原来只是你，加里……(喘)(喘)……别抓着我的胳膊！”",
        "Mysterium_Scene11": "'...Or I will visit you in your sleep!' / “……否则我会在你沉睡之时拜访！”",
        "Wumbus_Scene2": "Wumbus, always at ease, stretches out and enjoys the warmth of his planet's sun. / 温布斯，总是无忧无虑，身心放松，享受来自他星球的恒星带来的温暖。",
        "ZuzuCityExpress_Title": "The Zuzu City Express / 祖祖城特快列车",
        "MiracleAtColdstarRanch_Scene11": "That night, an unusual phenomenon... / 当晚，不寻常的现象发生了……",
        "Wumbus_Scene8": "But, despite having near-infinite entertainment options, Wumbus and his group of friends still enjoy gathering for a delicious meal of 'pizza' (formed from 100% gluten materials). / 但是，尽管拥有近乎无限的娱乐方式，温布斯和他的朋友们仍然喜欢聚在一起，享用一顿美味的比萨。（100% 由谷蛋白材料制成。）",
        "ItHowlsInTheRain_Title": "It Howls In The Rain / 它在雨中嚎叫",
        "ItHowlsInTheRain_Scene8": "Aiii!  / 哎呀！",
        "JourneyOfThePrairieKing_Scene5": "'Whoops! Looks like this avalanche is headed straight for the wagon train.' / “天哪！看起来这山崩是直冲着列车去的。”",
        "BraveLittleSapling_Scene5": "Fearing for his life, and demoralized by the relentless downpour, the brave little sapling begins to lose hope... / 恐惧从心中浮现，信念被无止尽的大雨冲刷殆尽，勇敢的小树苗开始失去希望……",
        "Mysterium_Scene2": "A faint silhouette in the dark... / 黑暗中若隐若现的轮廓……",
        "Mysterium_Description": "Peer behind the midnight veil... You must experience to believe! / 直面午夜面纱的背后所隐藏的……只有经历过才会相信！",
        "JourneyOfThePrairieKing_Scene10": "The wagon train is saved. / 列车获救了。",
        "NaturalWonders_Description": "Take a tour through the lands of the Ferngill Republic... from The Fern Islands to Zuzu City, this world is full of life! / 参观芬吉尔共和国的土地……从芬群岛到祖祖城，这个世界充满了生机！",
        "MiracleAtColdstarRanch_Scene5": "...But the family has run out of food. / ……但是这家人已经没有食物储备了。",
        "Wumbus_Scene6": "The movie is a humorous slice-of-life into Wumbus' strange world, a world where technology and society have 'advanced' to an extreme degree. / 这部电影描述的是温布斯生活的奇怪世界里的一个幽默的生活片段，这个世界的技术已经发展到了一个极高的水平。",
        "NaturalWonders_Scene3": "The warm climate of the southern ocean allows for extreme biodiversity... in short, the island is teeming with life! / 南大洋温暖的气候使得生物多样性极为丰富……简而言之，这个岛上充满了生命！",
        "Mysterium_Scene10": "'You MUST tell your friends to see MYSTERIUM tonight...' / “你一定要告诉你的朋友去看今晚的《神秘事迹》……”",
        "NaturalWonders_Title": "Natural Wonders: Exploring Our Vibrant World / 自然奇观：探索我们这充满活力的世界",
        "NaturalWonders_Scene8": "Finally, we return to the mainland, to visit one of the most pleasant areas of the continent... Stardew Valley. / 最后，我们回到大陆，参观大陆上最宜人的地区之一……星露谷。",
        "Wumbus_Scene1": "'Wumbus' / 《温布斯》",
        "Mysterium_Scene8": "A variety of disjointed, other-worldly scenes play out... / 各种支离破碎的，超脱世俗想象的场景上演……",
        "Mysterium_Scene5": "The desolate, unknown void of space... where untold horrors await. / 荒凉、未知的虚空中……有难以言说的恐怖在等待。",
        "BraveLittleSapling_Scene6": "...But what's this...? The sapling feels a tingling on the top of his head...  / ……但这是什么……？小树感到头顶有刺痛感……",
        "BraveLittleSapling_Title": "The Brave Little Sapling / 勇敢的小树苗",
        "ItHowlsInTheRain_Scene7": "'Look! It's in the bush...' / “看！它在灌木丛中……”",
        "BraveLittleSapling_Scene3": "The other saplings of his grove are gathered at the edge of town, excitedly waving their twigs goodbye...! / 树林里的其他小树聚集在城镇的边缘，激动地挥动着它们的树枝，与其告别……！",
        "NaturalWonders_Scene2": "The Fern Islands, a tropical paradise 80 miles off the southern coast. The islands formed due to volcanic activity in the region, and are still growing... / 芬群岛是南部海岸 80 英里外的热带天堂。这些岛屿是由于该地区的火山活动而形成的，而且还在不断增长……",
        "Mysterium_Title": "Mysterium / 神秘事迹",
        "JourneyOfThePrairieKing_Scene4": "'At last, I'll do away with that self-righteous sheriff and make off with the treasure... I deserve it!' / “终于能够把那个自以为是的治安官除掉并且把宝物偷走了……那是我的囊中之物！”",
        "NaturalWonders_Scene1": "'Natural Wonders: Exploring Our Vibrant World' / 《自然奇观：探索我们这充满活力的世界》",
        "BraveLittleSapling_Description": "An animated family comedy about a little sprout on a magical adventure to become a tree! / 一部家庭动画喜剧，讲述了一颗小树苗经历了一番神奇的冒险后成长为一棵树的故事！",
        "JourneyOfThePrairieKing_Scene3": "But, unbeknownst to our hero, the evil outlaw is watching from a nearby cliff... / 但是，我们的主人公不知道，邪恶的歹徒正在附近的悬崖上虎视眈眈……",
        "BraveLittleSapling_Scene7": "Perhaps a little rain was what it needed to begin its journey into becoming a tree! / 也许一场落雨就是迈向参天大树的第一步！",
        "MiracleAtColdstarRanch_Scene14": "The family is saved, and the spirit of hope is alive and well. The promise of the Winter Star is kept once again... / 一家人获救了，希望的精灵也活蹦乱跳着。冬星的诺言再一次被忠实地遵守……",
        "JourneyOfThePrairieKing_Scene2": "On the dusty old trail once again, we find Prairie King watching over a wagon train full of valuable treasure. / 又是在尘土飞扬的古道上，我们看到草原之王正看守着一列满载珍贵宝藏的货车。",
        "Wumbus_Scene4": "Wumbus tries to get his nephew, Rossel, interested in star-system culture and affairs, but Rossel is unimpressed. / 温布斯试图让他的侄子罗塞尔对星体系统的文化和事务感兴趣，但罗塞尔对此兴趣平平。",
        "ItHowlsInTheRain_Scene10": "It's still out there...  / 它还在那里……",
        "ItHowlsInTheRain_Scene6_2": "Agh!  / 啊！",
        "JourneyOfThePrairieKing_Scene6": "The Prairie King hears a faint rumbling in the distance... Look! / 草原之王听到远处传来一阵微弱的隆隆声……看！",
        "NaturalWonders_Scene7": "The island is known for its abundant population of raccoons! / 这个岛以其浣熊数量众多而闻名！",
        "MiracleAtColdstarRanch_Scene13": "They all shared the Stardrop fruit. Despite its small size, it was the most filling and delicious meal they'd ever had. / 他们一起分享了星之果实。尽管它很小，但却是他们吃过的最美味、最满足的食物。",
        "ZuzuCityExpress_Scene2": "The Zuzu City Express makes one final trip south, from the icy coast... It's a three day journey! / 祖祖城特快列车从冰冷的海岸向南部展开了最后一趟旅程……这是一趟为期三天的旅程！",
        "ItHowlsInTheRain_Scene8_2": "Oh...  / 哦……",
        "MiracleAtColdstarRanch_Scene12_2": "'We believed in the Winter Star, and so we were remembered!' / “我们相信着冬日星，正是因此我们得以被铭记！”",
        "MiracleAtColdstarRanch_Scene2": "It's the eve of The Winter Star, and it's been snowing for 3 weeks straight. / 这是冬星日的前夜，已经连续三周下雪不停了。",
        "JourneyOfThePrairieKing_Description": "The beloved video game comes to the silver screen! / 大受喜爱的电子游戏来到银屏之上！"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Strings/Notes",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "1": "...This is a book by Marnie.\n 'Animals are very sensitive. They like to be pet every day, and prefer to eat grass outdoors than dry hay. They don't like being outside in the rain, though. Happy animals produce higher quality products!' / ……这本书是玛妮的。\n“动物们非常敏感。它们喜欢每天都得到呵护。相比干草，它们更青睐户外的嫩草。然而，在雨天的时候它们不喜欢呆在外面。开心的动物会产出更高质量的产品！”",
        "11": "Mysteries Of The Dwarves\nThe Dwarves call themselves 'Smoluanu'... which translates to 'sky people'. An odd name for a group that lives deep underground, isn't it?\nAnother mystery of the dwarves is the advanced technology they supposedly possess. Evidence such as this had led me, despite the ridicule of my colleagues, to propose a new theory:\nI believe the dwarves are the remnants of a once advanced civilization whose interplanetary vehicle crashed on this planet long ago.\nI propose that this dwarvish spaceship bore down, deep underground... and over time, the dwarves became adapted to their new underground environment.\n My colleagues ask, 'Why didn't they come above ground and live on the surface?' ...Perhaps their old planet had a thicker atmosphere that protected them from stellar radiation, and they simply could not survive in our sunlight.\n That would explain why they only surface at night to take what they need from our houses...\n\n-M. Jasper / ——神秘的矮人——\n矮人自称“Smoluanu”……翻译过来就是“天空人”的意思。这对生活在地下深处的一群人来说是很奇怪的名字，不是吗？\n矮人的另一个神秘特点是他们与生俱来的先进技术。尽管同事们嘲笑我，根据这些证据我还是提出了一个新理论：\n我相信矮人是从前高度文明的幸存者，很久以前他们的星际交通工具在这个星球上撞毁。\n我认为这艘矮人飞船开始往地下钻孔，一直钻到地下深处……而随着时间的推移，矮人适应了新的地下生活环境。\n我的同事问：“他们为什么不来地上，不住在地表呢？……也许他们之前的行星有很厚的大气层保护他们不受恒星辐射，他们根本无法在我们的阳光下生存。\n这可以解释为什么他们只会在夜间出现在地面上活动，从我们的房子中取走他们需要的东西……\n\n-M.贾思博",
        "19": "Goblins / 哥布林^by M. Jasper^^The species commonly known as \"Goblin\" seems to have originated in the forests of the far northeast, beyond the Bluemire Hills. Characterized by their green skin, bright red eyes, and foul smell, initial encounters with Goblins can be frightening for unexperienced travelers.^^Despite their unsettling appearance, Goblins possess an intellectual and emotional capacity akin to humans, and have no trouble learning our customs and languages. The goblins I've met have been rather friendly and amiable, once I've shown that I mean no harm. Unfortunately, centuries of distrust and ill-treatment from humans has led many Goblins to pursue careers in the employ of witches, warlocks, necromancers, and other unsavory types.^^A traditional Goblin diet largely consists of grub meat, typically from the large and juicy grub varieties native to the Goblin home-forest. On special occasions, Goblins will indulge in an item called 'void mayonnaise'... considered perhaps the finest delicacy in all Goblin cuisine. / M.贾思博著^^这种被称作“哥布林”的生物起源于布鲁迈尔山另一侧的东北部森林。他们拥有着绿色的皮肤、亮红色的眼睛，并散发着恶臭，对于没有经验的旅行者来说，与他们初次相遇，会感到非常的可怕。^^尽管有着令人不安的相貌，但是，哥布林却拥有和人类相似的智慧和情感，对于学习我们的习俗和语言也没有任何障碍。我曾遇到过的哥布林，在我表示没有恶意之后，还是很友善和蔼的。不幸的是，由于几个世纪以来人们对他们的不信任和错误对待，很多哥布林开始投靠巫师、术士、死灵法师等等邪恶人士麾下效命。^^哥布林的传统食物大部分由蛆肉组成，这些蛆肉主要来源于哥布林家乡森林中的又大又肥的蛆。在特殊的场合，哥布林也会享用一种叫做“虚空蛋黄酱”的美食……这也许是哥布林菜谱中的最顶级菜肴了。",
        "3": "The Fisherman, Act I:\nTex: Gordy, how do you catch so many fish? For me, it takes forever!\nGordy: You must make the choice to become a true fisherman... and over time your fishing speed will increase!\nTex: So you're saying that improving my fishing skill will make me fish faster?\nGordy: Correct. One day you may even learn the secret to creating your very own bobbers, improving your mastery even more. Now, begone! / 渔夫，第一幕。\n泰克斯：戈尔迪，你是怎么钓到这么多鱼的？我怎么努力都做不到你那么厉害！\n戈尔迪：你必须选择成为职业渔夫……然后通过训练逐渐提升钓鱼的速度！\n泰克斯：所以你是说提高钓鱼技能就能加快钓鱼的速度？\n戈尔迪：是的。你甚至能掌握到制作浮标的技术，进一步提高捕鱼能力。话就到此了，你走吧！",
        "Missing": "There's a book missing here... / 这里少了一本书……",
        "12": "Highlights From The Book Of Yoba\n\nBefore time there was only the endless golden light.\n The light called out to itself...'Yoba'.\nYoba wanted more.\nYoba swirled the golden light into a vortex. Yoba swirled and swirled until a hole formed in the eye of the vortex.\nFrom this hole sprung a seed.\nYoba smoothed the golden light.\nYoba smoothed and smoothed, and the light became soil.\nInto this soil, Yoba planted the seed.\nThe seed sprouted, and behold! A vine sprung skyward, twisting and probing, casting a writhing shadow onto the golden void.\nAfter 11 days, the vine bore fruit.\nYoba, with knowing wisdom, peeled the tough skin off the fruit and saw that the world was inside.\nAnd so that is how the world came to be. / ——由巴之书摘录——\n\n在时间开始流动之前，天地间只有无边无际的金光。\n那光把自己叫做……“由巴”。\n由巴想要得到更多。\n由巴把金光搅拌成了一个漩涡。由巴转啊转啊转，直到漩涡的中央出现了一个大洞。\n这个洞里面诞生出了一粒种子。\n由巴让金光平静了下来。\n由巴让它不断地平静，平静，最终金光变成了土壤。\n由巴把种子埋在了这土壤之中。\n种子萌发了，看哪！一条藤蔓向着天空生长着、蜿蜒着、试探着，在金色的虚空之上留下一道蜿蜒的黑影。\n11 天之后，藤蔓结出了果子。\n由巴用他的智慧把果子坚硬的果皮剥了下来，并在里面看到了世界。\n世界就是这样形成的。",
        "10": "-~-Brewmaster's Guide-~-\n   Ah... to brew!\nThe rich smell of yeast wafting through a cedar loft... The floral overtones of freshly cut hops on a winter's eve... but I digress. You are probably more interested in the practical side of brewing...\nTo brew, you will need a keg. I'll leave it up to you to devise blueprints for a keg.\nKegs can be used to make several kinds of product. If vegetables are placed inside, the keg will produce juice. Juice takes the least amount of time to brew.\nIf wheat is placed in the keg, it will produce beer. Beer takes a while to brew, but it is quite profitable.\nPlacing hops in a keg will produce the beloved 'Pale Ale'\nPlace fruit in the keg to make wine. Wine takes the longest of all to make, but a wine made from the finest fruit is worth quite a bit!\nBe patient with your keg... you'll know it's finished when it's perfectly still. And only drink in moderation, or you'll surely regret it! / ——酿酒师指南——\n   啊……酿酒！\n酵母浓郁的香气从雪松阁楼中飘过……新伐木头的花一般的音调在冬季的夜晚起舞……但是我有点偏题了。你可能对酿酒的实用方面更感兴趣……\n如果要酿酒，你需要一个小桶。首先你需要有小桶的蓝图。\n小桶可以用来盛装多种产品。如果将蔬菜放在里面，小桶会产生蔬菜汁。蔬菜汁的酿造时间最短。\n如果将小麦放在桶里，会产生啤酒。啤酒需要一段时间来酿造，但它很能赚钱。\n将啤酒花放在小桶里将酿造深受喜爱的“淡啤酒”。\n将水果放在小桶中来酿造果酒。果酒的酿造时间最长，但是由最好的水果制成的果酒非常值得等待！\n对你的小桶保持耐心……当它完全静止时就酿好了。适量饮用，否则你一定会后悔的！",
        "14": "The Fisherman, Act II:\nTex: Gordy, tell me your best fisherman's story.\nGordy: *deep sigh*...I've caught a lot of big fish in my time...And some that are very rare and difficult...But there was one that I struggled to catch for three days and three nights\nGordy: I call this fish... 'The Legend'. He was a huge beast... And the harder I tugged on the line, the harder he tugged back. I let my guard down for a moment and he snapped my boat in two. I've never fished since.\nTex: Do you think anyone will ever catch him?\nGordy: Hmm... If this person were a master at fishing, and caught all other rare fish first, and made sure they ate the correct kind of food... then maybe. Above all you've got to have respect for the water, son.\nTex:...son? Do you mean... you're...\n ...f...father?\nGordy: Yes, my boy.\n\n**Dramatic Music as the curtains fall** / 渔夫，第二幕。\n泰克斯：戈尔迪，给我讲讲你最棒的有关渔夫的故事吧。\n戈尔迪：*叹气*……我以前可抓到过不少大鱼，有很多是很稀有很难抓的种类……但有一只鱼和我整整搏斗了三天三夜。\n戈尔迪：我将这鱼叫做……“传说之鱼”。那家伙个头很大……我越用力拉线，他也就越用力挣扎。我一走神，它就把我的船弄成了两半。在那之后我就再也没钓过鱼了。\n泰克斯：你觉得以后会有人抓住他吗？\n戈尔迪：唔……如果这人是个捕鱼大师，又抓到过所有稀有鱼类，还确保它们都得以正确喂养的话……也许会的吧。毕竟你要尊重水这种东西啊，儿子。\n泰克斯：……儿子……？难道你是……我父亲？\n戈尔迪：没错，我就是你父亲。\n\n**狗血的音乐响起**",
        "7": "The Secret of the Stardrop\n--\nFor thousands of years, people have been intrigued by the mysterious powers of the stardrop... but no one knows where they come from!\n Professor R. J. Kutler, a leading researcher on strange fruit, says this: 'We've discovered traces of genetic material on meteorites that closely resemble the Stardrop, but it's not a proven match'.\nRegardless of where they come from, the peculiar fruit is said to be uncommonly delicious... and some even claim they grant special power to those who eat them. / 星之果实的秘密\n——\n几千年以来，人们一直对星之果实的神秘力量感到好奇……但是从来没有人知道它们的来历。\nR.J.库特勒教授是奇异水果研究方面的领军人物，他是这么说的：“我们已经发现，陨石上面找到的遗传物质跟星之果实的遗传信息十分相似，不过未能证实两者是完全一致的。”\n无论它们来自何方，可以肯定的是这种奇妙的水果非常的美味……甚至传闻有人在吃了这些水果后获得了特殊的能力。",
        "20": "Solok Ulan Paa Eno Ra Coto Ulan Coto Ulan Mabo Bel Eno Ra Teba Omi Walo Nemo / 大象嚎叫 海上波涛 参加盛宴 镇上某处 里有乾坤^^Dop Ulan Coto Kui Mabo Awa Yoba Omi Solok Awa Lon Omi Omi Nemo^^Solok Teba Ra Awa Nemo Gawa Eno Bel Ulan Nemo Teba Omi Yoba Bel Omi Xi / ^鸭子闻声 蛋落下来 黄鹂远去 酱到他方 餐厅遗失 厅外有人^^奇闻古今 怪事连连 小声絮语 面面相觑 包罗万象 玩故习常 具体何事 箱里寻求",
        "18": "Note From Gunther: Wow, this library has really become great, thanks to your help! Thanks a bunch! / 冈瑟的字条：哇，这个图书馆真的变得不同凡响了，多亏了你的帮忙！非常感谢！",
        "16": "Secrets Of The Legendary Fish\n\nFishermen speak of five rare and unique fish that can only be caught by skilled anglers. Once caught, they will never appear again.\n\nThe crimsonfish lives in the warm ocean waters of summer. It's been sighted on the far eastern side of the beach.\n\nThe Glacierfish, which only appears in winter, can be caught off the southern tip of arrowhead island in Cindersap Forest... near where the river meets the ocean.\n\nThe Anglerfish has been spotted in fall, north of town where the river flows down from the mountains.\n\nThere's rumor of a strange, twisted fish that lives in the sewer.\n\n\n\nThe final fish, of a species never before caught, is known simply as 'legend'. It is rumored that he lives in a log submerged in the mountain lake, and only ventures out on rainy spring days to nibble at the frog's eggs. Only the most skilled fisherman can hope to catch this one.\n\nTrain at fishing and be persistent, and eventually you will catch these elusive fish. Make sure to respect the water and don't remove too many fish from the ecosystem. / ——传奇之鱼的秘密——\n\n渔夫们经常说起五只稀有而独特的鱼，只有经验极为丰富的渔人才能捕捉得到。一旦被抓住，这鱼就再也不会出现了。\n\n绯红鱼出没于夏日温暖的海洋之中。曾在海滩最东边被目击到。\n\n冰川鱼仅在冬天出没，出没于煤矿森林南端的箭头岛，森林与河流交汇处。\n\n鮟鱇鱼出没于秋季，城镇北方，河流从山上流下之处。\n\n据说还有一只奇怪诡异的鱼游走于下水道之中。\n\n\n\n最后一条鱼是属于一种从未被捕捉到过的物种，名为“传说之鱼”据说其生活在山上湖底一个沉入水中的木桩里，只在春季下雨时出来偷吃青蛙产的卵。只有技巧最为高超的渔人才能抓住这条鱼。\n\n钓鱼需要长期的锻炼，终有一日你会抓到这些稀有的鱼的。记住，保护生态平衡，不要过度捕鱼。",
        "0": "Tips On Farming--\n*Use fertilizer to improve quality, reduce workload, or hasten crop growth.\n*Fruit trees take a whole season to grow, but they require very little maintenance. Keep the area directly around your new sapling clear, or else it may not grow properly.\n*Crops will die as soon as the season ends, unless they grow in multiple seasons (e.g. Corn).\n*Some crops, such as kale and wheat, need to be harvested with the scythe. / 种植小贴士--\n*使用肥料有助于增加农作物质量、减少工作量、或提升农作物产量。\n*果树成熟需要一整个季节，但并不需要过多打理。注意要把树苗周围的杂草石木清理干净，以便果树茁壮成长。\n*各种庄稼在当前季节结束时，就会死去。除非是可以多季节进行栽培的种类，比如玉米。\n*诸如芥兰菜与大麦等部分农作物需要用镰刀来收割。",
        "9": "-- A Study On Diamond Yields --\n\n After years of research in the mines, I believe I've learned something about diamond frequency.\nMy research involved only the stones that are scattered about the mines...The ones that are broken with a pickaxe. Mineral yields from other sources require more research.\nDiamonds seem to only form at mine level 50 or greater. At level 50, approximately 1 in 500 stones will be diamond-rich.\n After level 50, the frequency of diamond formation seems to increase by about .000016 per level. Quite a rare gem!\n-M. Jasper / ——关于钻石生产的研究——\n\n经过我多年在矿井里的研究，我发现了一些关于钻石出现频率的规律。\n我的研究只涉及到矿井里面分布的那些石头……那些可以用镐头敲碎的石头。其他来源的矿产尚需进一步研究。\n钻石似乎只在 50 层或以上的矿井中形成。在 50 层时，大概每 500 块石头中就有 1 块矿石是富含钻石的。\n在 50 层以上，钻石出现的概率似乎以约每层 0.000016 的数值增加。真是一种罕见的宝石啊！\n——M·贾思博",
        "13": "Marriage Guide For Farmers\nBefore you ask someone to marry you, you'll have to date them for a while first (Ask someone to date you with a bouquet from Pierre's).\n When you're ready to pop the big question, you'll need to give them a 'Mermaid's Pendant'. Everyone knows what it means when you present them with one of those.\n It's rumored that on stormy days, the ghost of an old mariner appears in Stardew Valley, clutching just such a pendant.\n After the wedding ceremony, your partner will move in with you. Remember to treat your spouse well... They still like gifts even after marriage!\n\n(Paid for by Pierre) / ——农民结婚手册——\n在你向任何人求婚之前，你得先跟对方约会一段时间（用皮埃尔商店里面的花束来约会对象）。\n而在你求婚前，你得先准备一个“美人鱼吊坠”。所有人都知道这个吊坠所代表的意义。\n传说在狂风暴雨的日子，星露谷会出现一个老水手的鬼魂，其手中就是抓着这样的一个吊坠。\n在婚礼之后，你的伴侣会搬过来跟你一起住。记得要好好对待你的新婚伴侣……即使在结婚以后他们依然会喜欢收到礼物！\n\n（此文章由皮埃尔友情赞助）",
        "15": "Technology Report!\n\nThe blueprints for an advanced piece of machinery called a 'Crystalarium' have recently been published.\n This machine can grow crystals from almost nothing, providing their owners with endless supplies of valuable gems!\nHere's how it works: Place a gem of your choice inside the crystalarium...\nnow be patient, it can take up to several days... but eventually the crystalarium will grow a copy of whatever you placed inside!\nYou'll know it's ready when it stops wiggling. Once you remove your gem the crystalarium will start working on yet another clone... You'll never need to restock it unless you want to change the kind of gem it produces!\nUnfortunately, the crystalarium doesn't work with the extremely rare gemstone known as 'Prismatic Shard'... For some reason, the EMF from the shard interacts negatively with the crystalarium. / ——科技报告！——\n\n某种名为“宝石复制机”的先进科学机器的设计图纸已被发布。\n这个机器可以凭空种出水晶，为其拥有者提供源源不绝的贵重宝石！\n以下为使用说明：将选好的宝石放入机器之中……\n然后耐心等待，多日之后，宝石复制机便会将你放入的宝石完美复制！\n当机器停止抖动时，就证明工作完成了。在你取走宝石之后，宝石复制机便会继续复制宝石的工作……除非想要更改所生产的宝石种类，否则就无需更换原宝石！\n可惜的是，这机器无法复制极为稀有的“五彩碎片”宝石……不知为何，这种碎片的电动势对机器有所排斥。",
        "4": "  How deep do the mines go?\n This question has been pondered by many Stardew Valley explorers over the years... The truth is, no one really knows. Or at least, they aren't telling anyone.\nUnfortunately, many of those who venture deep into the mines never return...\nHowever, there have been a few bold adventurers who have traveled deep into the mines, and have resurfaced with interesting reports.\n Apparently, there are three distinct areas in the mine, each with unique monsters and treasures.\nSome adventurers speak of gigantic underground lakes and strange creatures... But none of these claims have been proven. / 矿井到底有多深？\n长久以来，星露谷的冒险者们都无法回答这个深奥的问题……其实，这个问题的答案无人知晓。\n有许多深入矿井探索的人都一去不复返……\n不过，有几名勇敢的探险老手真的抵达了矿井深处并平安返回。\n据他们所说，矿井主要分为三个不同的区域，每个区域都有对应的怪物与宝藏。\n有些冒险者自称发现了巨大的地下湖泊以及诡异的生物……不过至今也没人能够证明此事。",
        "5": "An old farmer's journal:\n I've been here for a year now, and I've started to make friends with the local townspeople. It sure feels great! And they're sending me gifts and secret family recipes in the mail, too! That's really helpful. / 一个老农民的日记：\n我搬来这里有一年了，我开始和当地居民交流起来。有朋友的感觉真好！他们送给我很多礼物，甚至包括他们珍藏的秘密家庭食谱！我受益良多。",
        "17": "...Saw something weird in the tunnel leading out from Pelican Town. There's a little door hidden in the dark. Couldn't get it open, though.\n\n-Gunther / ……我在出鹈鹕镇的隧道里看到了一些奇怪的东西。黑暗中有一扇小门。但我无法将其打开。\n\n——冈瑟",
        "2": "On Foraging\n The local woods and mountains are great places to find wild produce! A good forager will clear out any weeds, stumps, or stones from these areas, so the wild produce has plenty of space to grow!\nExpert foragers know the secret to cultivating wild food so that it can be grown on the farm. Isn't that amazing? / 当地的森林和山脉是寻找野生农作物的好地方！一名合格的采集者会时常清除这些区域的任何杂草、树桩或石头，让野生农作物有足够的生长空间！\n专家级采集者会懂得培育野生农作物的秘密，使它们可在农场生长。是不是很厉害？",
        "8": "Journey Of The Prairie King -- The Smash Hit Video Game!\n\nDid you know? Anyone who beats 'Journey Of The Prairie King' is automatically entered into a drawing for a special prize!\n\nDid you know? The developer has stated that the protagonist is based on a real-life character... A true cowboy hero from a prairie-island in the Gem Sea! / 草原王者大冒险——超热门电子游戏！\n\n你知道吗？任何通关“草原王者大冒险”的玩家都会自动进入到一个特别奖励的抽奖环节。\n\n你知道吗？游戏开发者说主角取材于一个真实的人物……一位来自宝石海上的大草原岛的牛仔英雄！",
        "6": "'Scarecrows'\n Once you start growing a lot of crops on your farm, you can expect to be visited by crows. In the morning, you might discover that a crow has made breakfast out of your hard work!\nOne way to prevent those bothersome crows from eating your crops is to set up scarecrows near your crops.\nBe aware that scarecrows have limited range, so you'll need multiple if your farm is large.\nScarecrows keep track of how many crows they've diverted. You can use that to tell if they're in a useful spot.\n\n* 'Collectible Scarecrows' aren't just for looks! They work just the same as the regular model. / “稻草人”\n一旦开始在农场上种植大面积的庄稼，你就得准备好迎接乌鸦的拜访。每天早上，你都有可能发现一只只乌鸦把你辛苦换来的劳动果实当作早餐饱餐一顿了！\n想要避免这些烦人的乌鸦吃掉你的庄稼，其中一种方法就是在庄稼旁边放置稻草人。\n请注意，稻草人的保护范围是有限的。如果你的农场很大的话，你就需要多放置几个稻草人。\n稻草人会记录它们一共吓走了多少只乌鸦。你可以据此判断稻草人是否置放在了最有效的位置上。\n\n* “稻草人收藏系列”可不仅仅是用来观赏的！它们也能像正常的稻草人那样发挥作用。"
      }
    },
