        "Acorn_Description": "This can be planted to grow an oak tree. / 可以种出一棵橡树。",
        "GlassShards_Description": "A mixture of glass shards smoothed by centuries of ocean surf. These could have belonged to an ancient mosaic or necklace. / 被几个世纪海浪冲刷光滑的玻璃碎片混合物。可能是古代拼花装饰或者项链上的东西。",
