        "Arrowhead_Description": "A crudely fashioned point used for hunting. / 用于打猎的粗制尖状物。",
        "Stone_Node_Description": "Break apart to obtain stone, ores, or geodes. / Break apart to obtain stone, ores, or geodes.",
        "Coleslaw_Description": "It's light, fresh and very healthy. / 口味清淡、新鲜，还很有益健康。",
        "MixedSeeds_Description": "There's a little bit of everything here. Plant them and see what grows! / 各种种子都有一点。种下它们，看看长出来什么东西！",
        "Powdermelon_Name": "Powdermelon / 霜瓜",
        "AquamarineRing_Name": "Aquamarine Ring / 海蓝宝石戒指",
        "StoneFloor_Description": "Place on the ground to create paths or to spruce up your floors. / 放在地上修建小路，也可以装饰地板。",
        "Geminite_Name": "Geminite / 杰明石",
        "IronStone_Name": "Iron Stone / Iron Stone",
        "Ginger_Description": "This sharp, spicy root is said to increase vitality. / 这种根茎味道辛辣，据说可以提高活力。",
        "Slime_Name": "Slime / 史莱姆泥",
        "RottenPlant_Description": "Decomposing organic material. It's slimy and unpleasant. / 分解有机物质。黏稠且还不好闻。",
