        "Book_Roe_Description": "Fishing treasure chests have a chance to yield roe. / 钓鱼宝箱有几率开出鱼籽。",
        "Hardwood_Description": "A special kind of wood with superior strength and beauty. / 一种特殊的木材，有更高的强度和观赏性。",
        "CauliflowerSeeds_Name": "Cauliflower Seeds / 花椰菜种子",
