        "ElvishJewelry_Name": "Elvish Jewelry / 精灵珠宝",
        "Ectoplasm_Name": "Ectoplasm / 灵外质",
        "Pizza_Description": "It's popular for all the right reasons. / 受欢迎是很合理的事。",
        "AdvancedTVRemote_Description": "It has more buttons than a regular remote. Perfect for the avid TV watcher! / 比一般的遥控器按键更多。专为资深电视迷设计！",
        "SlimeCharmerRing_Name": "Slime Charmer Ring / 史莱姆克星戒指",
        "VampireRing_Description": "Gain a little health every time you slay a monster. / 每次杀死一个怪物后获得一点生命值。",
        "Mudstone_Description": "A fine-grained rock made from ancient clay or mud. / 有细密的纹理，是上古的粘土或者泥巴变成的。",
        "MapleSeed_Name": "Maple Seed / 枫树种子",
        "Wool_Description": "Soft, fluffy wool. / 柔软蓬松的羊毛。",
        "FiddleheadRisotto_Description": "A creamy rice dish served with sauteed fern heads. It's a little bland. / 香软的米饭拌上清炒的蕨菜芽。汤有点淡。",
        "PrismaticShard_Name": "Prismatic Shard / 五彩碎片",
        "MagmaCap_Description": "A very rare mushroom that lives next to pools of lava. / 一种非常罕见的蘑菇，生长在熔岩池旁。",
        "LuckyPurpleShorts_Description": "Better not inspect these too closely. / 最好别细看。",
        "TruffleOil_Description": "A gourmet cooking ingredient. / 佳肴必备的原料。",
        "DwarfScrollIII_Name": "Dwarf Scroll III / 矮人卷轴 III",
