        "Oyster_Name": "Oyster / 牡蛎",
        "CactusFruit_Description": "The sweet fruit of the prickly pear cactus. / 尖刺仙人掌的甜美果实。",
        "PrehistoricSkull_Name": "Prehistoric Skull / 史前头骨",
        "Ghostfish_Description": "A pale, blind fish found in underground lakes. / 一种在地下湖里能找到的苍白色的盲鱼。",
        "SavageRing_Description": "Gain a short speed boost whenever you slay a monster. / 当你杀死一个怪物后获得一点加速。",
        "LargemouthBass_Description": "A popular fish that lives in lakes. / 一种住在湖里的受欢迎鱼类。",
        "FrozenTear_Name": "Frozen Tear / 泪晶",
        "Bixite_Description": "A dark metallic Mineral sought after for its cubic structure. / 黑色的金属矿石。有着四四方方的结构。",
        "StoneBase_Description": "A simple block of stone. / 石头组成的简单区块。",
