        "Book_Woodcutting_Name": "Woody's Secret / 伐木秘事",
        "RainbowTrout_Name": "Rainbow Trout / 虹鳟鱼",
        "JukeboxRing_Description": "Plays a random assortment of music you've heard. / 随机播放你已听过的音乐类型。",
        "ArtifactTrove_Name": "Artifact Trove / 古物宝藏",
        "Diamond_Description": "A rare and valuable gem. / 一种稀有且贵重的宝石。",
        "Melon_Name": "Melon / 甜瓜",
        "SpeedGro_Name": "Speed-Gro / 生长激素",
        "PepperSeeds_Description": "Plant these in the summer. Takes 5 days to mature, and continues to produce after first harvest. / 夏天播种。5 天成熟，收获之后还能继续结果。",
        "MelonSeeds_Description": "Plant these in the summer. Takes 12 days to mature. / 夏天播种。12 天成熟。",
        "Daffodil_Description": "A traditional spring flower that makes a nice gift. / 一种传统的春天花朵，适合送礼。",
        "Sprinkler_Description": "Waters the 4 adjacent tiles every morning. / 每天早上给四块邻近的土地浇水。",
        "IridiumStone_Description": "Break apart to obtain iridium ore. / Break apart to obtain iridium ore.",
        "SolarEssence_Description": "The glowing face is warm to the touch. / 发光的表面摸起来很温暖。",
        "Pumpkin_Name": "Pumpkin / 南瓜",
        "Wood_Description": "A sturdy, yet flexible plant material with a wide variety of uses. / 结实而有韧性的植物材料，有非常广泛的用途。",
        "Bruschetta_Name": "Bruschetta / 意式烤面包",
        "StrangeDoll_Name": "Strange Doll / 诡异玩偶",
        "WildPlum_Name": "Wild Plum / 野梅",
        "GlacierfishJr_Name": "Glacierfish Jr. / 小冰川鱼",
        "Bruschetta_Description": "Roasted tomatoes on a crisp white bread. / 盖上烤西红柿的酥脆白面包。",
        "OrnamentalFan_Description": "This exquisite fan most likely belonged to a noblewoman. Historians believe that the valley was a popular sixth-era vacation spot for the wealthy. / 这把精致的扇子很有可能属于一个贵妇人。历史学家认为星露谷是第六纪元富人的度假胜地。",
        "SmallGlowRing_Description": "Emits a small, constant light. / 发出微小而又恒定的光。",
        "SmallMagnetRing_Description": "Slightly increases your radius for collecting items. / 些许增加你收集物品的半径。",
        "AgedRoe_Name": "Aged Roe / 腌鱼籽",
        "Book_Riding_Description": "You gain a little extra speed when riding a horse. / 骑马速度稍微加快。",
        "CorkBobber_Description": "Slightly increases the size of your \"fishing bar\". / 稍微增加你的“钓鱼条”的大小。",
        "Jade_Name": "Jade / 翡翠",
        "Clam_Description": "There's a chewy little guy in there... / 有东西曾在这里面住过。",
        "Dorado_Name": "Dorado / 麻哈脂鲤",
        "HyperSpeedGro_Description": "Greatly stimulates leaf production. Guaranteed to increase growth rate by at least 33%. Mix into tilled soil. / 促进叶子生长。保证能让植物的生长速度加快 33% 以上。使用时加到犁过的土地中。",
        "WrigglingWorm_Name": "Wriggling Worm / 蠕动蚯蚓",
        "OceanStone_Name": "Ocean Stone / 海洋石",
        "DuckEgg_Description": "It's still warm. / 还热乎着呢。",
        "Coral_Name": "Coral / 珊瑚",
        "AmethystRing_Name": "Amethyst Ring / 紫水晶戒指",
        "FiberSeeds_Name": "Fiber Seeds / 纤维种子",
        "SummerSquashSeeds_Description": "Plant in the summer. Takes 6 days to grow, and continues to produce after first harvest. / 夏天播种，6 天长成，收获之后还能继续结果。",
        "BlueberryTart_Name": "Blueberry Tart / 蓝莓千层酥",
        "SummerSpangle_Description": "A tropical bloom that thrives in the humid summer air. Has a sweet, tangy aroma. / 一种热带花朵，生长于潮湿的夏日季节。拥有芬香刺鼻的味道。",
        "Book_WildSeeds_Description": "Weeds have a greater chance to yield mixed seeds. / 杂草有更大的几率掉落混合种子。",
        "DeluxeFertilizer_Name": "Deluxe Fertilizer / 顶级肥料",
        "Sugar_Description": "Adds sweetness to pastries and candies. Too much can be unhealthy. / 加入面团中可以使小点心更加酥甜。吃多了对健康无益。",
        "DeluxeRetainingSoil_Name": "Deluxe Retaining Soil / 顶级保湿土壤",
        "Wine_Flavored_(O)282_Name": "Cranberry Wine / ",
        "DinosaurMayonnaise_Description": "It's thick and creamy, with a vivid green hue. It smells like grass and leather. / 粘稠且呈乳脂状，带有鲜艳的绿色。闻起来有草和皮革的味道。",
        "Honey_Flavored_Name": "{0} Honey / {0}蜂蜜",
        "FossilizedSpine_Name": "Fossilized Spine / 脊柱化石",
        "MixedFlowerSeeds_Name": "Mixed Flower Seeds / 混合花卉种子",
        "Eel_Description": "A long, slippery little fish. / 一种长而滑溜的小鱼。",
        "BeanStarter_Name": "Bean Starter / 青豆种子",
        "WeddingRing_Description": "An old Zuzu City tradition... It's used to ask for another farmer's hand in marriage. / 祖祖城的古老传统……用来向另一位农夫求婚。",
        "JojaCola_Description": "The flagship product of Joja corporation. / Joja 公司的旗舰产品。",
        "GoldenRelic_Name": "Golden Relic / 黄金遗物",
        "Bullhead_Description": "A relative of the catfish that eats a variety of foods off the lake bottom. / 鲶鱼的近亲，以湖底的多种食物为食。",
        "BarbedHook_Description": "Makes your catch more secure, causing the \"fishing bar\" to cling to your catch. Works best on slow, weak fish. / 上钩的鱼更不容易跑掉，使“钓鱼条”靠紧猎物。对速度慢、弱小的鱼最有效。",
        "FossilStone_Name": "Fossil Stone / Fossil Stone",
        "Jamborite_Name": "Jamborite / 绿水镍矿",
        "GoldenRelic_Description": "It's a golden slab with hieroglyphs and pictures emblazoned onto the front. / 是一个黄金板，它的正面刻绘着象形文字和图画。",
        "Sardine_Description": "A common ocean fish. / 一种常见的海鱼。",
        "SmokedFish_CollectionsTabDescription": "A whole fish, smoked to perfection. / 一整条鱼，烟熏风味恰到好处。",
        "Book_Bombs_Name": "Dwarvish Safety Manual / 矮人安全手册",
        "PinaColada_Description": "Drink in moderation. / 请适度饮酒。",
        "QualityFertilizer_Description": "Improves soil quality, increasing your chance to grow quality crops. Mix into tilled soil. / 提高土壤品质，增加你种出高品质作物的可能性。使用时加到犁过的土地中。",
        "OakResin_Name": "Oak Resin / 橡树树脂",
        "Pyrite_Description": "Commonly known as \"Fool's Gold\". / 常被称为“蠢材的黄金”。",
        "RabbitsFoot_Description": "Some say it's lucky. / 有人说它会带来好运。",
        "Goby_Description": "Some types of Gobies can climb up waterfalls. / 有些虾虎鱼能攀上瀑布。",
        "CrispyBass_Description": "Wow, the breading is perfect. / 哇哦，裹上面包屑简直完美。",
        "MangoStickyRice_Name": "Mango Sticky Rice / 芒果糯米饭",
        "BlackberryCobbler_Name": "Blackberry Cobbler / 黑莓脆皮饼",
        "LifeElixir_Description": "Restores health to full. / 恢复全部的生命值。",
        "Crimsonfish_Name": "Crimsonfish / 绯红鱼",
        "GarlicSeeds_Name": "Garlic Seeds / 大蒜种子",
        "Driftwood_Description": "A piece of wood from the sea. / 从海里漂来的一块木头。",
        "CauliflowerSeeds_Description": "Plant these in the spring. Takes 12 days to produce a large cauliflower. / 春天播种。12 天后长成大花椰菜。",
        "Broccoli_Name": "Broccoli / 西蓝花",
        "VoidGhostPendant_Name": "Void Ghost Pendant / 虚空幽灵吊坠",
        "Aerinite_Name": "Aerinite / 青泥石",
        "Book_Speed_Description": "You run a little bit faster. / 你的跑步速度变快了一点。",
        "RustySpur_Name": "Rusty Spur / 生锈的靴刺",
        "MermaidsPendant_Description": "Give this to the person you want to marry. / 把它送给你未来的伴侣。",
        "Weeds_FiberOrMixedSeeds_Ugly_Name": "Weeds / 杂草",
        "VoidMayonnaise_Description": "A thick, black paste that smells like burnt hair. / 粘稠、膏状，闻起来像烧焦的头发。",
        "NapalmRing_Name": "Napalm Ring / 燃烧弹戒指",
        "JadeRing_Name": "Jade Ring / 翡翠戒指",
