        "BrownOveralls_Name": "Brown Overalls / 棕色背带裤",
        "HeartShirt_Description": "Wear your heart on your sleeves with this extra soft garment. / 把你的爱心穿在这超软的衣袖上。",
        "OilStainedShirt_Description": "It's already stained with oil for that greasy look. / 本来就沾满了油，所以看起来油腻腻的。",
        "GingerOveralls_Description": "The color scheme is inspired by ginger ale. / 配色的灵感来自姜汁汽水。",
