        "NavyTuxedo_Description": "An elegant top for formal events. / 正式场合穿的考究上衣。",
        "OrangeBowShirt_Name": "Orange Bow Shirt / 橘红色领结衫",
        "CopperBreastplate_Name": "Copper Breastplate / 铜胸甲",
        "OrangeShirt_Description": "An orange shirt. / 橘黄色的上衣。",
        "NavyTuxedo_Name": "Navy Tuxedo / 藏青色无尾礼服",
        "StarShirt_Description": "The star is supposed to glow in the dark, but it doesn't. / 这颗星星本应该在黑暗中闪闪发光，然而并没有。",
        "BlueHoodie_Description": "A sporty blue pullover with a hood. / 蓝色的带兜帽套头衫，颇有运动风。",
