      "Entries": {
        "OptionsPage.cs.11292": "Inventory Slot #4 / 物品栏格 ＃4",
        "Utility.cs.5857": "Journey Of The Prairie King (Ending) / 普瑞尔国王的旅程（结束）",
        "Game1.cs.3118": "+{0} Health / +{0} 生命值",
        "ShopMenu.cs.11478": "Sorry about the smell. / 这味道很难闻，抱歉了。",
        "TV.cs.13120": "Select channel: / 选择频道：",
        "StrengthGame.cs.11695": "Goldfish / 金鱼",
        "OptionsPage.cs.11274": "Controls: / 控制：",
        "GrandpaStory.cs.12036": "When that happens, my boy, you'll be ready for this gift. / 等那一天到来的时候，我亲爱的孙子，你就可以打开这个礼物了。",
        "SlayMonsterQuest.cs.13735": "Mama throwing a fit / 妈妈发脾气了",
        "Farmer.cs.2010": "Nice try... / 没门……",
        "Up": "Up / 向上键",
        "Options.cs.4564": "Windowed / 窗口",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13300": "I'm in the market for / 我来超市是为了",
        "Options_ToggleAnimalSounds": "Mute Animal Sounds / 关闭动物声音",
        "NPC.cs.4278": "It's my birthday and you give me this? Is this some kind of joke?$s/It's my birthday and you give me this? Is this some kind of joke?$s / 今天我生日，你居然送我这个？你是在开玩笑吗？$s/今天我生日，你居然送我这个？是在开玩笑吗？$s",
        "Options.cs.4557": "Music Volume / 音乐音量",
        "ResourceClump.cs.13962": "Looks like you'll need an upgraded axe to destroy this gnarled old log. / 你需要升级斧头才能摧毁这根粗糙的原木。",
        "Utility.cs.5369": "When @ first arrived in Pelican Town, no one knew if she'd fit in with our community...#$b#But from this day forward, @ is going to be as much a part of this town as any of us!$h#$b#It is my great honor on this day {0} of {1}, to unite @ and %spouse in the bonds of marriage. / @刚到鹈鹕镇时，没人知道她是否能融入我们的社区……#$b#但从今以后，@将成为我们中的一员！$h#$b#我非常荣幸在这{1} {0}的一天，宣布@和%spouse喜结连理。",
        "ShopMenu.cs.11500": "I smuggled these goods out of the Gotoro Empire. Why do you think they're so expensive? / 我从戈特洛国走私出了这些货物。你为什么认为他们很贵？",
        "movie_classic": "The Zuzu City Express Theme / 祖祖城特快列车主题",
        "ShopMenu.cs.11471": "Looking to sell any metals or minerals? / 想卖点矿物或者金属吗？",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13364": "I have a craving for {0}. Please bring one by for me. / 我超想吃{0}。请带给我一份吧。",
        "NPC.cs.4065": "Good evening / 晚上好",
        "MapPage.cs.11114": "Secret Woods / 秘密树林",
        "Object.cs.12691": "A female slime has hatched. / 已孵化一只雌性史莱姆。",
        "Event.cs.1524": "$q -1 null#Well, should we start the dance now? / 那我们现在就开始跳舞吗？#$r -1 0 yes#Yes, let's start. / 是的，让我们开始吧。#$r -1 0 no#Not yet. / 还没有。",
        "Event.cs.1164": "Received 2000g  / 收到 2000 金",
        "NPC.cs.4449": "Being a parent is annoying, sometimes...  I just don't feel like getting up.$a / 有时候当父母是件很让人烦心的事……我只是不想起床。$a",
        "CraftingRecipe.cs.574": "Wild Seeds (Any) / 野生种子（任意）",
        "MapPage.cs.11119": "Railroad / 铁路",
        "Utility.cs.5835": "Fun Festival / 欢乐节",
        "Game1.cs.3685": "Stardew Valley has crashed... / 星露谷已崩溃……",
        "MapPage.cs.11107": "Fish Shop / 鱼店",
        "NPC.cs.4126": " You could really make him happy with that. /  送他这个会让他非常开心的。",
        "OnlyPlaceOnFarm": "Can only be placed on the Farm. / 只能布置在农场。",
        "NPC.cs.4084": " loves '{0}'? / 喜欢“{0}”？",
        "Event.cs.1688": "Read my fortune (100g) / 算算我的未来（100 金）",
        "TutorialMenu.cs.11813": "Construction / 施工",
        "NPC.cs.4293": "Ow! I can't believe you would do that to me!$s / 嗷！我不敢相信你居然会这样对我！$s",
        "TV.cs.13199": "The spirits are in good humor today. I think you'll have a little extra luck. / 精灵们今天的心情很不错。你今天要走运了。",
        "Raft.cs.14204": "Raft / 筏",
        "SlayMonsterQuest.cs.13733": "wigglers.  / 扭动的小东西。",
        "Farmer.cs.2003": "{0} Level Up / {0}升级",
        "NPC.cs.4171": " I'm not sure why. /  我不知道为什么。",
        "Dialogue.cs.740": "too close to / 太接近",
        "Event.cs.1259": "I finished writing my book, and it's a sci-fi novel! Remember when you told me you were a fan of sci-fi?$h#$b#Behold, '%book'. It's about a boy who forms a symbiotic partnership with a semi-telepathic lifeform. Together they unravel the dark mysteries of an interstellar cabal.$u#$b#I -almost- feel like I should split the profits with you, considering how much help you gave me!$h / 我写完了我的书，它是一本科幻小说！还记得你告诉我你是科幻小说的粉丝吗？$h#$b#看，'%book'。这本书讲的是一个与半心灵感应的生命形成共生伙伴关系的男孩的故事。他们一起解开星际阴谋的黑暗之谜。$u#$b#想到你给了我那么多帮助，我几乎觉得我应该分些利润给你！$h",
        "Buff.cs.471": "Invincible / 无敌",
        "Dialogue.cs.737": "with / 与",
        "Utility.cs.5823": "Library And Museum / 图书馆和博物馆",
        "Dialogue.cs.698": "Bitter / 苦的",
        "Event.cs.1243": "dog / 狗",
        "Object.cs.13074": "Blueprints for crafting {0} / 用于制造{0}的设计图",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13557": "I will < you forever if you bring me {0}!     -Haley / 如果你能带给我{0}，我会永远倾慕你！——海莉",
        "GrandpaStory.cs.12051": "Dear {0}, / 亲爱的{0}，^^If you're reading this, you must be in dire need of a change.^^The same thing happened to me, long ago. I'd lost sight of what mattered most in life... real connections with other people and nature. So I dropped everything and moved to the place I truly belong.^^^I've enclosed the deed to that place... my pride and joy: {1} Farm. It's located in Stardew Valley, on the southern coast. It's the perfect place to start your new life.^^This was my most precious gift of all, and now it's yours. I know you'll honor the family name, my boy. Good luck.^^Love, Grandpa^^P.S. If Lewis is still alive say hi to the old guy for me, will ya? / ^如果你在读这封信，你一定身处困境期待转机。^^很久以前，我也遇到过相同的情况。当时的我对人生中最重要的东西视而不见……那就是人与人之间的联系以及人与自然之间的关系。所以我放弃了一切，并来到了真正属于我的地方。^^^我将那块地的契据放在了信封里……那里寄托了我所有的骄傲和愉悦：{1}农场。它坐落在星露谷，在南海岸。它将是你开启新生活的完美之地。^^这是我最珍贵的礼物，现在它是你的了！我知道你会光宗耀祖的，我亲爱的孙子。祝你好运。^^爱你的，祖父^^顺便说一句，如果刘易斯还活着，你就替我向那个老家伙问好吧，好吗？",
        "RandomSentence.11": "The Courageous Quail grilled far, far away from the other Quail / 勇敢的鹌鹑远离其他的鹌鹑，在远处被烧烤",
        "Sleep": "Sleep / Sleep",
        "NPC.cs.3927": "Your house should be ready tomorrow. / 你的房子明天应该可以完工。",
        "MineCart.cs.12115": "Best:  / 最佳：",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13306": "Could a local farmer deliver one to me? / 当地农夫可以送我一个吗？",
        "TV.cs.13187": "Partially cloudy with a light breeze. Expect lots of pollen! / 部分地区多云，并伴有微风。空气中会有大量花粉！",
        "Event.cs.1785": "You've already bought everything in the shop! / 你已经把商店里的货全部买光了！",
        "FarmComputer_PiecesHay": "Pieces Of Hay: {0}/{1} / 干草：{0}/{1}",
        "Dialogue.cs.808": "/silvery / 银色",
        "Dialogue.cs.716": "Crisp / 薯片",
        "Event.cs.1845": "Now I see you, middle-aged, walking through town at dusk. You pause at a window to see a family having dinner. You hang your head and hurry off into the darkness. / 现在我看到已到中年的你于黄昏时刻在镇上散步。您停在一户人家的屋窗前，看他们享受晚餐。你垂下你的头，匆匆离开，走进暗夜。",
        "Dialogue.cs.687": "Gloomy / 阴暗的",
        "SaveGameMenu.cs.11381": "Saving / 正在储存",
        "Event.cs.1811": "Ahh... yes. I see you at the beach. There's some kind of event taking place. You walk up to {0} and say something funny... Hmmm... It seems like you two are good friends. / 啊……是的，我在海滩上看到你了。当时那里好像正在举行什么活动，你走向{0}然后说了些很逗乐的笑话……嗯……你们俩好像是很好的朋友。",
        "TV.cs.13117": "The Queen Of Sauce (Re-run) / 酱料女皇（重播）",
        "CalicoJack.cs.11972": "Bet: {0} / 赌注：{0}",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13500": "I need {0} to rub on my sore {1}. / 我需要{0}来擦下我那疼痛的{1}。",
        "CalicoJack.cs.11958": "Dealer's closer to {0} / 庄家更接近 {0}",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13482": " Will pay a flat rate on delivery. /  交货时会统一付费。",
        "BrowserStop": "BrowserStop / 浏览器停止",
        "StrengthGame.cs.11680": "Leather Boot / 皮靴",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13544": "$h#$b# ...Let's see. Here's what I owe you. / $h#$b#……好的。这是我应该付给你的。",
        "Event.cs.1851": "The crystal ball has moved on... I see you in a golden room... grinning about something. Oh, I see... You're playing some kind of game and you just can't lose! / 水晶球中的景象发生了改变……我看到你在一个金色的房间中……你正对着什么东西咧嘴笑。原来如此……你在玩某种游戏，并且你不能输！",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13381": "...feel like {0} for some reason. Please bring to Sebastian at 24 Mountain Road. / ……不知为什么，我想要{0}。请把这个带到山路 24 号的塞巴斯蒂安。",
        "RightControl": "RightControl / 右 Control",
        "CalicoJack.cs.11930": "Double Or Nothing / 加倍赌注来一次",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13324": "Feeling gloomy... {0} might cheer me up.     -Sebastian / 我感觉有些抑郁。也许{0}能让我精神振作起来。－塞巴斯蒂安",
        "NPC.cs.4182": "{0} hates '{1}'. You don't want to know the details. Trust me. / {0}讨厌“{1}”。至于原因你还是不知道的好，相信我。",
        "Game1.cs.3046": "Thu / 星期四",
        "NPC.cs.3962": "...!! I'll accept this. Thank you.$l#$e#I didn't know you felt the same.$l/...!! I'll accept this. Thank you.$l#$e#I didn't know you felt the same.$l / ……！！我很乐意接受。谢谢。$l#$e#我不知道你也有和我一样的感受。 $l/……！！我很乐意接受。谢谢。$l#$e# 我不知道你也有和我一样的感受。$l",
        "StrengthGame.cs.11670": "Tree Trunk / 树干",
        "MilkPail.cs.14176": "{0} is too young to produce milk. / {0}太小了还不能产奶。",
        "Language.5": "Chinese / 中文",
        "NPC.cs.4439": "I wonder how much the new baby will change things?$s / 我不知道婴儿的出现会让我们的生活发生什么变化？$s",
        "FishingQuest.cs.13261": " small motorcycle! / 小摩托车",
        "FishingQuest.cs.13264": "n encyclopedia set! / 套百科全书！",
        "StrengthGame.cs.11682": "Hardened Clay / 硬化粘土",
        "Options.cs.4562": "Resolution / 分辨率",
        "Dialogue.cs.739": "away from / 远离",
        "StrengthGame.cs.11698": "Alfredo Sauce / 阿尔弗雷多酱汁",
        "ShopMenu.cs.11583": "Out of stock / 缺货",
        "Left-Click": "Left-Click / 左键点击",
        "NPC.cs.4433": "Don't you have work to do?$a / 你不是还有工作需要处理吗？$a",
        "Utility.cs.5381": "Life is going to be different from now on... / 人生从此将展开新的一页。",
        "Dialogue.cs.741": "dangerously close to / 危险距离",
        "FarmComputer_TotalOpenHoeDirt": "Open Tilled Soil: {0} / 开耕土壤：{0}",
        "Debris.cs.621": "Copper / 铜",
        "Dialogue.cs.682": "Green / 绿色",
        "NPC.cs.4097": "If you want {0} to like you, give her '{1}'. / 如果你想赢得{0}的爱，送给她“{1}”。",
