        "GameLocation.cs.8709": "Deluxe Pack / 豪华背包",
        "HorseFlute_InvalidLocation": "You cannot summon your horse here. / 你无法在此处召唤马。",
        "SkillsPage.cs.11600": "+{0} Pickaxe Efficiency / +{0} 十字镐功效",
