        "Utility.cs.5730": "Aerobics Class / 有氧健身课",
        "SkillsPage.cs.11589": "Club Card / 会员卡",
        "RandomSentence.6": "The Gigantic Submarine floated uncomfortably close to the Mermaid / 巨大的潜艇浮十分靠近美人鱼",
        "Nauseous_BuffName": "Nauseated / 恶心",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13577": "Hey, thanks a million, @! I should've known you'd be the one to take this job.$h / 嗨，太感谢了。@！我早该料到你是会接下这份工作的人。$h",
        "TV.cs.13201": "This is rare. The spirits feel absolutely neutral today. / 这可罕见了。精灵们今天很冷漠。",
        "Dialogue.cs.799": "/deep blue / 深蓝色",
        "NPC.cs.4424": "I just don't have any energy today.$s / 我只是今天没什么精神。$s",
        "SkillsPage.cs.11588": "Rusty Key / 生锈的钥匙",
        "ShopMenu.cs.11514": "Welcome to the Stardrop Saloon! What can I get ya? / 欢迎来到星之果实酒吧！想来点什么吗？",
        "FishingQuest.cs.13235": "overfishing of their competitor species allowed them complete access to their favorite food. / 由于它们的竞争物种被过度捕捞，因此它们可以轻易的获得自己想要的食物。",
        "Event.cs.1723": "Congratulations! You won 1st place with a rating of {0}!#$b#Your prize is 1000 star tokens! Spend them wisely.$h#$b#Oh, and don't forget to clean out your grange display box. / 恭喜！你赢得了第一名，得分是{0}！#$b#你的奖品是 1000 星星币！省着点花。$h#$b#哦，别忘了清理你的农庄展览箱。",
        "Game1.cs.3101": ".  / 。 ^^Your maximum energy level has increased. / ^你的最大能量等级提升了。",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13597": " Hmm... this isn't as exciting as I thought it would be...$s#$b#But that's not your fault! Haha. Thanks for responding to my bulletin, @.$h / 嗯嗯……并不像我想象的那么有意思……$s#$b#但不是你的错！哈哈，谢谢你回复我的公告板，@。$h",
        "NPC.cs.4516": "Darling / 亲爱的",
