        "Event.cs.1635": "I'm sorry... I already have a partner. / 不好意思……我已经有一个舞伴了。",
        "junimokart_ghostmusic": "Junimo Kart (Ghastly Galleon) / 祝尼魔赛车（恐怖大帆船）",
