        "DayTimeMoneyBox.cs.10378": "Paused / 暂停",
        "Event.cs.1306": "The farm hasn't changed much all that much since we last spoke... but that's okay.#$b#If you're enjoying your new life, that's all that matters to me...#$b#I must return to the other world, now... but feel free to call on me again when you're ready. / 自从我们上次谈过之后，这个农场并没发生太大变化……但没关系。#$b#只要你能幸福快乐的生活，我就满足了……#$b#现在我必须回到另一个世界去……如果你准备好了随时都可以再联系我。",
        "OptionsPage.cs.11234": "Auto Run / 自动奔跑",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13566": "Oh! That's exactly what I needed! Heehee! I'm so happy!$h / 噢！这正是我需要的！嘻嘻！我太高兴了！$h",
        "Buff.cs.453": "Burnt / 烧伤",
