        "SpecialItem.cs.13090": "Under a piece of wood, you found a {0}! You're not sure what it's for, but it seems important. It's been added to your wallet. / 在一块木头下，你找到了一把{0}！你不太确定这是做什么用的，但它看上去很重要。它已添加到你的钱包中。",
