        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13489": " I could use one. /  我需要来一个。",
        "Boots.cs.12500": "Level {0} / 等级 {0}",
        "Event.cs.1838": "Hmmm... now what's this young lady's name? ... I believe it starts with an '{0}'. / 嗯嗯……那么这位年青女士叫什么名字呢？……她的名字应该是以“{0}”开头的。",
