        "Multiply": "Multiply / 乘号键",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13370": "SO hungry. Need {0}. / 太饿了。需要{0}。",
        "Object.cs.12929": "I've scared off {0} crows. / 我已经吓走了 {0} 只乌鸦。",
        "NPC.cs.4462": "I got up early and watered some crops for you. I hope it makes your job a little easier today. / 今天起得早，就顺便给你的作物浇了点水。希望这样能让你今天的工作轻松一些。",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13390": "stir-fry / 小炒",
