        "Event.cs.1758": "Leave the {0}? Once you do, the festival will end. / 确定要离开{0}吗？一旦你选择离开，节日就会结束。",
        "NPC.cs.4149": "If you want {0} to dislike you, give him '{1}'. He hates it with a passion. / 如果你想{0}讨厌你，送给他“{1}”。他超恨这东西。",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13349": "serve for dinner tonight / 成为今晚的晚餐",
        "SocializeQuest.cs.13786": "Hey! Will someone say 'Hi' to everyone in town for me? I want to spread a message of {0} today!   -Emily / 嘿！镇上有人愿意替我和所有人打招呼吗？我今天想给每个人传个口信，内容是{0}！——艾米丽",
        "MapPage.cs.11064": "{0} Farm / {0}农场",
