        "KeyToTheTown_desc": "Allows access to all buildings in town, at any time of day. / 用它可以随时进入镇上的所有建筑。",
        "Utility.cs.5732": "Winter (Nocturne Of Ice) / 冬季（冰之夜曲）",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13462": "Hi! I need {0} for a new appetizer I'm thinking about. Drop one off at the saloon and I'll be very grateful.     -Gus / 嗨！我需要{0}来做我的新开胃菜。只要放一个在酒吧，我就会非常感激的。－盖斯",
