        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13571": "${Looking for a buddy to bring me {0}.       -Sam¦I would like a cute girl to bring me {0}.  ( / ${在寻找一个朋友给我送{0}。——山姆¦我想让一个美女给我送{0}。(^_-)      -Sam}$ / _-) ——山姆}$",
        "summer": "summer / 夏季",
