        "junimokart_whalemusic": "Junimo Kart (The Gem Sea Giant) / 祝尼魔赛车（宝石海巨人）",
        "Event.cs.1848": "The crystal ball has moved on... AH! You're in combat! There's something dreadful bearing down on you from the dark, but you seem more than ready to face it. / 水晶球中的景象发生了改变……啊！你在战斗！黑暗中有可怕的东西正准备压倒你，但你似乎做好了充足的准备。",
