        "FishingRod.cs.14082": "Length: / 长度：",
        "WateringCan_enchant": "In your hands, this can will never run out of water. / 在你的手中，这个罐子会有倒不完的水。",
        "Event.cs.1872": "{0}, with {1} big, slimy fish! / {0}，和 {1} 条大型而生猛的鱼！",
        "NPC.cs.4020": "That's right. Now step aside, blockhead. / 那就对了。现在靠边站，笨蛋。",
