        "OptionsPage.cs.11243": "Sound Volume / 音效音量",
        "Game1.cs.3095": "It's strange, but the taste reminds you of  / 很奇怪，但那个味道让你想起 ",
        "NPC.cs.4089": "She told me.$h / 她跟我说的。$h",
        "NPC.cs.4452": "I need some alone time... Why don't you take care of the kids for a change?$a / 我需要一些独处的时间……今天由你照顾孩子如何？$a",
        "Dialogue.cs.751": "Point Drake / 点点公鸭",
        "Event.cs.1315": "The farm hasn't changed much in these past few years... but that's okay.#$b#If you're enjoying your new life, that's all that matters to me... / 这几年这个农场没改变多少……但没关系。#$b#只要你享受你的新生活，我就满足了……",
