        "Event.cs.1732": "Hi there, @. You got 4th place with a score of {0}.#$b#Your reward for participating is 50 star tokens. Hey, maybe you'll do better next year.$h#$b#Oh, and don't forget to clean out your grange display box. / 你好，@。你是第 4 名，得分是{0}。#$b# 作为参与的奖励，你将得到 50 个星星币。也许明年你能获得更好的名次。$h#$b#哦，别忘了清理你的农庄展览箱。",
        "SaveGameMenu.cs.11378": "Your progress has been saved. / 你的进度已保存。",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13455": "nasal drip / 滴鼻法",
        "ShopMenu.cs.11513": "Hungry? Thirsty? I've got just the thing. / 饿了？渴了？我这里正好有能满足你食欲的东西。",
