        "Event.cs.1695": "You don't have enough money to pay my fee... What a shame. / 你没有足够的钱来支付我的费用……真可惜。",
        "NPC.cs.3963": "...You want to get more serious? I feel the same way.$l#$e#I'm kind of nervous. Aren't you?$l / 你想让我们的感情更进一步吗？我再赞同不过了。$l#$e#我稍微有些紧张呢。你也是吧？$l",
