        "NPC.cs.4279": "Oh... It's for my birthday? ... Thanks.$s/Oh... It's for my birthday? ... Thanks.$s / 噢！是给我的生日礼物吗？……谢谢。$s/噢！是给我的生日礼物吗？……谢谢。$s",
