        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13497": "I'm running low on {0}. If someone could bring me one, it would be much appreciated. / 我的{0}不太够了。如果谁能带一个给我，我将十分感激。",
        "FishingQuest.cs.13231": "Thanks, @!$h#$b#The {0} population was getting out of hand because {1} / @，谢谢你！$h#$b#{0}的数量已然失控了，因为{1}",
        "Event.cs.1760": "Maybe for you, but not for me! You're not going to understand...  Just... go away.$7#$b#...Ugh...$7#$b#Wait...$7 / 也许对你来说是这样，但对我来说可并非如此！你不会明白的……你走开。$7#$b#……呃……$7#$b#等等……$7",
