        "Junimo.cs.6625": "Bai! / 再见！",
        "Event.cs.1847": "The crystal ball has moved on... I see you somewhere dark... but there you are, inspecting a marvelous gemstone! It's glittering in the light of a small lantern. / 水晶球中的景象发生了改变……我看到你在黑暗的地方……你正在观察一块奇妙的宝石！它在小灯笼的微光下闪闪发亮。",
        "Dialogue.cs.809": "/glimmering/gold / 闪烁金色",
        "Event.cs.1846": "The crystal ball has moved on... Now I see you harvesting a plump, ripe melon. You're on a wonderful looking farm, bursting with life! / 水晶球中的景象发生了改变……现在，我看到你正收割成熟的大甜瓜。你在一个很漂亮的农场里，浑身上下都散发着活力！",
        "StrengthGame.cs.11697": "Toothpick / 牙签",
