        "NPC.cs.4420": "*sigh*...$s / *叹气*……$s",
        "DesertTrader4_female": "The camel seems to like you, miss. That is indeed a very good sign. / 骆驼好像很喜欢你，小姐。这真是吉兆。",
        "ResourceCollectionQuest.cs.13658": "Great. / 非常好。",
        "Game1.cs.3159": "Drink {0}? / 要喝掉“{0}”吗？",
        "NPC.cs.4443": "I'm pregnant... can't you make your own breakfast?$s / 我怀孕了……你能不能自己做早餐？$s",
        "Debris.cs.630": "Quartz / 石英",
        "Event.cs.1504": "It's nothing fancy, but it's the best I could afford. / 虽然不是什么贵重物品，但这是我能买得起的最好的东西了。",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13539": " I really appreciate it. /  对此，我真的非常感激。",
