        "Backslash": "Backslash / 反斜杠",
        "OptionsPage.cs.11242": "Music Volume / 音乐音量",
        "TitleMenu.cs.11733": "You've started the game 1000 times! / 你已经玩了 1000 次。",
        "Event.cs.1834": "Ooo... It's dark, and I see you and a certain young lady. She looks quite hopeful, and eager to spend time with you. / 噢……太暗了，我看见你和一个年轻女士。她看上去充满期待，但很渴望与你共度时光。",
        "Event.cs.1656": "Leave / 离开",
        "TV.cs.13191": "The spirits are furious. Apparently someone tried to give them a worthless offering... Hmm. It's unwise to play jokes on the spirits! / 精灵们暴怒异常。显然是某些人打算给他们一些烂贡品……跟精灵开玩笑可不明智！",
        "Event.cs.1738": "$q -1 null#...Yes? / ……什么事？#$r -1 0 danceAsk#(Ask {0} to be your dance partner) / （邀请{0}作你的舞伴）#$r -1 0 null#Never mind... / 没事……",
        "NewLostAndFoundItems": "Some items were placed in the town Lost and Found. / 失物招领处有新的物品。",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13590": "Bored... could someone bring me {0}?    -Abby / 无聊……谁能给我带点{0}吗？－阿比盖尔",
        "Utility.cs.5373": "@... %spouse... #$b# As the mayor of Pelican Town, and regional bearer of the matrimonial seal, I now pronounce you husband and wife!$h / @……%spouse……#$b#作为鹈鹕镇的镇长，以及本区婚姻负责人，我现在宣布你们结为夫妻！$h",
        "Utility.cs.5746": "Fall (The Smell Of Mushroom) / 秋季（蘑菇的味道）",
        "Event.cs.1741": "Give {0} her secret gift? / 要把神秘礼物交给{0}吗？",
        "Dialogue.cs.721": "Submarine / 潜艇",
        "NPC.cs.4276": "Oh, is it my birthday today? I guess it is. Thanks. This is nice.$h/Oh, is it my birthday today? I guess it is. Thanks. This is nice.$h / 今天是我的生日吗？嗯，看来是这样呢。谢谢。挺不错的。$h/今天是我的生日吗？嗯，看来是这样呢。谢谢。挺不错的。$h",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13507": "toe / 脚趾",
        "Event.cs.1681": "Try your hand at some fishing? You could win big. / 想试试钓鱼吗？你没准能赢大奖哦。",
        "PurchaseAnimalsMenu.cs.11344": "Lives in the barn. / 饲养在畜棚里。",
        "Event.cs.1634": "You want to be my partner for the flower dance?#$b#Okay! I'd love to.$h / 你愿意成为我的花舞舞伴吗？#$b#好的！我很乐意。$h",
        "Event.cs.1821": "Ahh... Indeed. I see you in a room, having a conversation with a lady. / 啊……的确。我看到你在一个房间中和一位女士交谈。",
