        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13538": " Thanks so much! /  太谢谢啦！",
        "Event.cs.1063": ", and  / ，和 ",
        "NPC.cs.4489": "I figured the room could use a little more decoration. / 我觉得房间可以再进行下装饰。",
        "Utility.cs.5825": "A Golden Star Is Born / 金色明星的诞生",
        "ResourceClump.cs.13948": "Your axe isn't strong enough to break this log. / 你的斧头不够锋利，无法劈开这根原木。",
        "Krobus_AfterWedding": "Good morning, @... I snuck in during the night.$l#$b#It'll take me a while to get used to this new life... This is very different from the sewers... / 早上好，@……我是晚上悄悄进来的。$l#$b#我需要一段时间才能适应这种新生活……这跟住在下水道区别很大。",
        "OpenBrackets": "OpenBrackets / 左括号",
        "NPC.cs.4091": "Here's a secret, {0} loves '{1}'. / 跟你说个秘密。{0}喜欢“{1}”。",
        "Event.cs.1316": "You've done a good job with the place.#$b#It seems you've tried your best... that's all I can ask for. I'm proud of you. / 你把农场修建的不错。#$b#看上去你已经尽了全力……我只能要求那么多了。我为你感到骄傲。",
