        "Dialogue.cs.796": "/green / 绿色",
        "MapPage.cs.11090": "Graveyard / 墓园",
        "ResourceCollectionQuest.cs.13659": "#$b#Hmm... It seems these ores don't have any rare gems hidden inside. That's okay.#$b#Here's your ores back, and your payment... as promised. / #$b#嗯嗯……看来并没有珍稀的宝石藏在那些矿石中。没关系。#$b#矿石还给你，还有你的报酬……我们说好的。",
        "Utility.cs.5682": "Fall / 秋季",
        "Event.cs.1501": "Hi. So, I'm your secret gift-giver this year.#$b#Well? Open it! / 嗨。今年由我来给你准备神秘礼物。#$b# 还犹豫什么？快打开吧！",
        "SlayMonsterQuest.cs.13740": "dress / 款式",
        "Utility.cs.5927": "Dairy Cow / 乳牛",
        "DiaryEvent.cs.6667": "...We're becoming good friends. I hope things stay that way. / ……我们之间的关系越来越好了。我希望这种友谊能一直持续下去。",
        "Dialogue.cs.699": "Dragon / 龙",
        "Dialogue.cs.722": "ran / 奔跑",
