        "NPC.cs.4103": "If you want to get on {0}'s good side, give her '{1}'. / 如果你想赢得{0}的支持，送给她“{1}”。",
        "GrandpaStory.cs.12038": "When that happens, my dear, you'll be ready for this gift. / 等那一天到来的时候，我亲爱的孙女，你就可以打开这个礼物了。",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13465": "on my shelf / 我的书架上",
        "Event.cs.1829": "Now I see you and {0} in a dimly lit room. You look serious... but not unhappy. Something important must be happening. / 现在我看到你和{0}在一个昏暗的房间里。你看上去很严肃……但也不是不高兴。一定有什么重要的事情要发生了。",
        "Event.cs.1827": "Now I see you and {0} in a field of grass. You seem happy. / 现在我看到你和{0}在草地里。你看上去很开心。",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13516": " Please bring one ASAP!! / 请尽快带给我一个！！",
        "TitleMenu.cs.11723": "Watch TV shows to learn useful tips, cooking recipes, and more! / 观看电视节目学习有用的建议、烹饪食谱以及更多内容！",
