        "TV.cs.13128": "Ah... I sense that a new viewer has joined us. A young man from... Stardew Valley? Welcome, welcome! / 啊……我感觉到一个新观众加入了我们。一个从……星露谷来的年轻人？欢迎，欢迎！",
