        "ShopMenu.cs.11501": "I'll have new items every week, so make sure to come back! / 我这里每周都有新货到，你记得多回来看看！",
        "ShopMenu.cs.11474": "I can upgrade your tools with more power. You'll have to leave them with me for a few days, though. / 我能让你的工具变得更加好用。但你得把这些工具在我这儿放几天。",
