        "Dialogue.cs.717": "Wig / 假发",
        "FishingQuest.cs.13256": "Hey, you succeeded, @!$h#$b#The {0} is an exciting catch, don't you think?  / 嘿，你成功了，@！$h#$b#{0}是个令人兴奋的收获，你不觉得吗？ ",
