        "ResourceCollectionQuest.cs.13647": "I am looking for someone to bring me {0} {1}s{2}    -Clint / 我在找能给我带 {0} 个{1}的人{2} ——克林特",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13469": "on my great-grandfather's tombstone / 我曾祖父的墓碑上",
        "MeleeWeapon.cs.14138": "+{0} Accuracy / +{0} 命中率",
