        "Event.cs.1803": "Not a valid gift. / 礼物无效。",
        "NPC.cs.4116": " She loves that stuff. /  她喜欢这些东西。",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13504": "back / 后背",
        "ImeNoConvert": "ImeNoConvert / ImeNoConvert",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13560": "${Looking for a handsome young man to bring me {0}.       -Haley / ${在寻找一个帅哥，希望他能给我送来{0}。－海莉^FOR GIRLS ONLY: psst... I need {0}... you know what it's for. Keep it secret, okay?      -Haley}$ / 女孩们注意了：嘘……我需要{0}……你知道它是用来干什么的。请严守秘密，好吗？－海莉}$",
        "JunimoNoteMenu.cs.10783": "Rewards / 奖品",
        "Utility.cs.5367": "When @ first arrived in Pelican Town, no one knew if he'd fit in with our community...#$b#But from this day forward, @ is going to be as much a part of this town as any of us!$h#$b#It is my great honor on this day {0} of {1}, to unite @ and %spouse in the bonds of marriage. / @刚到鹈鹕镇时，没人知道他是否能融入我们的社区……#$b#但从今以后，@将成为我们中的一员！$h#$b#我非常荣幸在这{1} {0}的一天，宣布@和%spouse喜结连理。",
        "Farmer.cs.2021": "Planter / 种植者",
        "TV.cs.13190": "It's going to snow all day. Make sure you bundle up, folks! / 一整天都要下雪。一定要多穿些，伙计们！",
        "MapPage.cs.11070": "Leah's Cottage / 莉亚的农舍",
