        "Dialogue.cs.752": "Minister Valley / 牧师谷",
        "DiaryEvent.cs.6670": "...I like her more than just a friend. / ……我很喜欢她，在我眼中，她比朋友更重要。",
        "Object.cs.12996": "You found a peculiar statue behind Grandpa's Shrine. / 你在爷爷的神龛后面找到一个特殊的雕像。",
