        "NPC.cs.3970": "You're strange.$s / 你真奇怪。$s",
        "NPC.cs.4490": "I was going to do some decorating today, but I changed my mind.$a / 我今天本来想装饰房子的，但是改变主意了。$a",
        "Object.cs.12856": "Fertilizer / 化肥",
