        "SlayMonsterQuest.cs.13723": "Wanted: Slime hunter to slay {0} {1} / 悬赏：希望找一位史莱姆猎人去击败 {0} 只{1} ",
        "PrintScreen": "PrintScreen / PRINT SCREEN 键",
