        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13446": "A paste of fresh {0} makes a wonderful tonic for {1}. If you find one, I could put it to good use.       -Dr. Harvey  / 新鲜的{0}可以作为{1}的滋补品。如果你找到了，就把它交给我，我能很好地利用它。－哈维医生 ",
