        "GameLocation.cs.8175": "It's locked. / 锁上了。",
        "NPC.cs.4141": "{0} really hates '{1}'! He told me.$h / {0}非常讨厌“{1}”！他跟我说的。$h",
        "Language.6": "Portuguese / 葡萄牙语",
        "Object.cs.12854": "Fruit / 水果",
        "ResourceCollectionQuest.cs.13649": ", to aid in the understanding of local minerals. / ，以帮助理解当地的矿物。",
        "Event.cs.1257": "I finished writing my book, and it ended up being a mystery novel! Remember when you told me you were into mystery?$h#$b#Behold, '%book', a thrilling tale of deception and intrigue!$u#$b#I -almost- feel like I should split the profits with you, considering how much help you gave me!$h / 我写完了我的书，它是一本悬疑小说！还记得你告诉过我你对悬疑小说很着迷吗？$h#$b#看， '%book'，一个惊心动魄的关于欺骗和阴谋的故事！$u#$b#想到你给了我那么多帮助，我几乎觉得我应该分些利润给你！$h",
        "NPC.cs.4448": "{0}, can't you tell? You're pregnant.$l / {0}，你看不出来吗？你怀孕了。$l",
        "MapPage.cs.11179": "Tunnel / 隧道",
        "RandomSentence.8": "The Gloomy Elf danced atop the Tomb / 忧郁的精灵在墓顶上跳舞",
