        "MapPage.cs.11073": "2 Willow Lane / 2 柳巷",
        "TV.cs.13136": "Welcome to KOZU 5... your number one source for weather, news, and entertainment. / 欢迎来到 KOZU 5 ……这里是您获取天气、新闻和娱乐资讯的第一选择。^And now, the weather forecast for tomorrow... / 现在播报明天的天气预报……",
        "JunimoNoteMenu.cs.10786": "We    the  Junimo are    happy to    aid  you.  In     return we     ask for gifts   of      the valley.    If you   are one     with    forest   magic    then you    will   see    the true    nature   of  this scroll. / We    the  Junimo are    happy to    aid  you.  In     return we     ask for gifts   of      the valley.    If you   are one     with    forest   magic    then you    will   see    the true    nature   of  this scroll.",
