        "RandomSentence.14": "The Lonely Puppet ran far, far away from the Planet / 孤独的木偶远远的跑开，远离了行星",
        "NPC.cs.4063": "Good morning / 早上好",
        "ResourceCollectionQuest.cs.13667": "#$b#I like to inspect local ores from time to time, to keep track of quality and abundance.#$b#Let me just take a look at these... Hmm... I see.#$b#Thank you. You can keep these ores. They're of {0} quality. / #$b#我喜欢时不时的查看一下当地的矿石，这样可以持续记录矿石的质量和数量的历史数据。#$b#让我看一下这些…喔…我明白了。#$b#谢谢你，你可以留着这些矿石。他们的质量为{0}。",
        "NPC.cs.4466": "Good Morning, {0}!  / 早上好啊，{0}！ ",
        "LeftShift": "LeftShift / 左 Shift",
        "Event.cs.1652": "Step right up! Pick a color and place your bet for a chance to double your wager! / 勇敢些！挑选一种颜色然后投注吧，即有机会让您的赌注加倍！",
        "MapPage.cs.11105": "JojaMart / Joja 超市",
        "Event.cs.1317": "You've done well, my boy. / 你干得很出色，我的孩子。^You've done well, my dear.#$b#%farm Farm has never looked better. It's an honor to the family name.#$b#Grandpa is pleased. / 你干得很出色，我亲爱的。#$b#%farm农场从没这么美过。这是很值得自豪的事情。#$b#爷爷非常高兴。",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13458": "migraines / 偏头痛",
        "Furniture_Decoration": "Decoration / 装饰",
        "NPC.cs.4021": "!!! Is... is that a 'Club Card'? / ！！！是……是一张“会员卡”吗？",
        "TutorialMenu.cs.11809": "Mining / 采矿",
