        "Event.cs.1633": "You want to be my partner for the flower dance?#$b#Okay. I look forward to it.$h / 你愿意成为我的花舞舞伴吗？#$b#好的。我很乐意。$h",
        "FarmComputer_Intro_Farm": "{0} Farm Analysis: / {0}农场报告：",
