        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13466": "above the mantle / 斗篷上",
        "Game1.cs.3160": "Eat {0}? / 要吃掉“{0}”吗？",
        "NPC.cs.4060": "Hello. / 你好。",
        "Event.cs.1308": "You've done well, my boy. / 你干得很出色，我的孩子。^You've done well, my dear.#$b#%farm Farm has never looked better. It's an honor to the family name.#$b#Grandpa is pleased.#$b#I must return to the other world, now... but feel free to call on me again when you're ready. / 你干得很出色，我亲爱的。#$b#%farm农场从没这么美过。这是光宗耀祖的事情。#$b#爷爷非常高兴。#$b#我现在必须回到另一个世界去了……但只要你准备好了随时都可以再联系我。",
        "Select": "Select / 选择",
        "NPC.cs.3959": "Uh... This is awkward. Look, I don't really know you that well...$s / 啊……太尴尬了。看，我真的不太了解你……$s",
        "Dialogue.cs.802": "/chocolate/brown / 褐色",
