        "Options.cs.4556": "Auto Run / 自动奔跑",
        "Utility.cs.5931": "Requires construction of a Barn / 需要修建畜棚",
        "PurchaseAnimalsMenu.cs.11349": "Happy adults provide goat milk every other day. A milk pail is required to harvest the milk. / 快乐的成年山羊每隔一天都会产奶。需要奶桶来盛这些奶。",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13555": "Ah, the item I requested.#$b#Your work was satisfactory. Here is your compensation. / 啊，这正是我想要的物品。#$b#你的工作令人满意。这是你的报酬。",
        "ShopMenu.cs.11469": "Too lazy to mine your own ore? No problem. / 懒得挖掘自己的矿石？没问题。",
