        "Game1.cs.3044": "Tue / 星期二",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13420": "roast up for dinner tonight / 烘烤今晚的晚餐",
        "TV_Fishing_Channel_rainy": "rainy days / 雨天",
        "Fresh_Prefix": "Fresh {0} / 新做的{0}",
        "FishingQuest.cs.13234": "careless fishermen released way too many for a local tournament. / 粗心的渔民为了进行当地的比赛而排放了太多垃圾。",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13303": " a delicious {0}.  /  一个美味的{0}。",
        "Shears.cs.14247": "{0} has no wool right now. / {0}现在没有羊毛。",
        "Utility.cs.5750": "Fall (Raven's Descent) / 秋季（乌鸦的祖先）",
        "Dialogue.cs.732": "grilled / 烧烤",
        "Dialogue.cs.730": "smelled / 闻",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13488": " I can't get enough of them! /  它们真让我爱不释手！",
        "CapsLock": "CapsLock / Caps Lock 键",
        "NPC.cs.3966": "What? Didn't you just ask someone else to marry you? You're crazy!$s / 什么？你刚才不是已经向别人求婚了吗？你疯了！$s",
        "Game1.cs.3689": "Loading... / 正在加载……",
        "Event.cs.1663": "Leave / 离开",
        "TV.cs.13183": "It's going to be clear and sunny all day. / 全天都会风和日丽，万里无云。",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13476": "Looking for {0} to make into buttons for a dress I'm making. If you find one could you bring it to me?.     -Emily / 寻找{0}来做我裙子上的扣子。如果你找到一个的话，能带给我吗？－艾米丽",
        "Event.cs.1548": "$q -1 null#Are you ready to participate in the ice fishing competition? / 你准备参加冰钓比赛吗？#$r -1 0 yes#Yes. / 是。#$r -1 0 no#Not yet. / 还没有。",
        "Buff.cs.468": "Warrior Energy / 战士能量",
        "SkillsPage.cs.11592": "+{0} Hoe Efficiency / +{0} 锄头功效",
        "StrengthGame.cs.11688": "Trout / 鳟鱼",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13422": "dry for next winter / 晾干，明年冬天再用",
        "Game1.cs.3099": "Your mind is filled with thoughts of... ConcernedApe? (Well, thanks!) / 你的头脑里充满了各种想法……都是关于 ConcernedApe 的想法？（非常感谢！）",
        "MapPage.cs.11111": "Open all day / 全天开放",
        "NPC.cs.4507": "Pookie / 布奇",
        "Home": "Home / Home 键",
        "Object.cs.12783": "Requires 10 Wood / 需要 10 块木头",
        "movietheaterafter": "Movie Theater (Closing Time) / 电影院（闭院时间）",
        "NPC.cs.4441": "{0}, I filed our adoption papers. Now all we can do is cross our fingers and wait.$l / {0}，我提交了我们的领养文件。现在，我们只能祈祷并耐心等待。$l",
        "PurchaseAnimalsMenu.cs.11343": "Adults can be milked daily. A milk pail is required to harvest the milk. / 成年奶牛每天都能产奶。需要奶桶来盛这些奶。",
        "TV_Fishing_Channel": "Fishing Info / 钓鱼信息",
        "OptionsPage.cs.11300": "Inventory Slot #12 / 物品栏格 ＃12",
        "Utility.cs.5371": "@... %spouse... #$b# As the mayor of Pelican Town, and regional bearer of the matrimonial seal, I now pronounce you husband and... well, husband!$h / @……%spouse……#$b#作为鹈鹕镇的镇长，以及本区婚姻负责人，我现在宣布你们成为彼此的伴侣！$h",
        "SlayMonsterQuest.cs.13767": "Ah, @! So you helped us with our monster problem? Thank you!$h#$b#I hope you didn't go through too much trouble... / 啊，@！你帮助我们解决了怪物问题？非常感谢！$h#$b#我希望你之前没有遇上太大的麻烦……",
        "ResourceCollectionQuest.cs.13674": "Hello! It's Robin. Could someone bring me {0} pieces of {1}? They need to be fresh... that means gathered today. Thanks! / 你好！我是罗宾。谁能给我 {0} 块{1}呢？我需要新鲜的……也就是必须得是今天采摘的，谢谢了！",
        "StrengthGame.cs.11663": "Bulldozer / 推土机",
        "StrengthGame.cs.11700": "Skim Milk / 脱脂牛奶",
        "EraseEof": "EraseEof / EraseEof",
        "CraftingRecipe.cs.570": "Vegetable (Any) / 蔬菜（任意）",
        "RenovationBlocked": "Remove all items from the renovation area. / 从装修区域中取出所有物品。",
        "Event.cs.1729": "Hi there, @. It looks like you won 3rd place with a rating of {0}.#$b#Your prize is 200 star tokens! Spend them wisely.$h#$b#Oh, and don't forget to clean out your grange display box. / 你好，@。你好像赢得了第三名，得分是{0}。#$b#你的奖品是 200 星星币！省着点花。$h#$b#哦，别忘了清理你的农庄展览箱。",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13320": "Howdy neighbors! I want to try giving my cows {0} to increase their milk production. If you find one could you swing it by for me?.     -Marnie / 好心的邻居们！我想给我的奶牛{0}以增加它们的牛奶产量。如果你找到了能顺便带给我一个吗？－玛妮",
        "NPC.cs.4094": "If you want {0} to like you, give him '{1}'. / 如果你想赢得{0}的爱，送给他“{1}”。",
        "NPC.cs.4164": "If you want to play a cruel joke on {0}, give her '{1}'. She might not forgive you, though. / 如果你想和{0}开个残忍的玩笑，可以送给她“{1}”。不过她可能不会原谅你。",
        "Crsel": "Crsel / Crsel",
        "OptionsPage.cs.11279": "Use Tool / 使用工具",
        "Insert": "Insert / INSERT 键",
        "Utility.cs.5754": "Winter Festival / 冬季庆典",
        "LoadGameMenu.cs.11023": "Really delete file: {0}? / 真的要删除文件吗：{0}？",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13599": " Heh heh... perfect. Here's your reward, @. Don't say a word to my Dad. $h / 嘿嘿……完美。这是你的报酬，@。不要跟我的爸爸说。$h",
        "VolcanoShop4": "This mountain was the home of my ancestors. Now we live in the ruins of their great civilization. / 我的祖先世世代代住在这座山上。现在我们生活的地方不过是他们伟大文明的遗迹。",
        "SlayMonsterQuest.cs.13757": "creatures / 动物",
        "TreeFertilizer1": "Already Mature / 已经成熟",
        "Utility.cs.5845": "A Sad Story / 一个悲伤的故事",
        "Fishing_Channel_Intro": "Thank you for tuning in to F.I.B.S., the Fishing Information Broadcast Service. Despite our unfortunate name, you can rest assured that we provide only the most trustworthy information about this season's fishing opportunities. / 感谢您收听 F.I.B.S. 钓鱼信息广播服务。请您相信，我们绝不是来钓鱼的，我们只会向您提供本季节捕鱼时机的最可靠的消息。",
        "BrowserSearch": "BrowserSearch / 浏览器搜索",
        "Farmer.cs.2031": "Greenhorn / 新手",
        "Dialogue.cs.693": "Rubbery / 橡胶似的",
        "Game1.cs.3210": "not using gamepad / 不使用游戏手柄",
        "OptionsPage.cs.11297": "Inventory Slot #9 / 物品栏格 ＃9",
        "Event.cs.1662": "Play (50g) / 游戏（50 金）",
        "Wallpaper.cs.13206": "Decorates the walls of one room. / 装饰一间房间的墙面。",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13387": "salad / 沙拉",
        "IslandTrader4_female": "Please trade wiz me, sister... / 请跟我做个生意，姐妹……",
        "ShopMenu.cs.11504": "Beautiful country you have here. One of my favorite stops. The pig likes it, too. / 这里真的是风景绝佳。是我最喜欢的目的地之一。猪也很喜欢这里呢。",
        "Event.cs.1857": "You added {0} to the soup. / 你往汤里加了一个{0}。",
        "Event.cs.1307": "You've done a good job improving the place since we last spoke.#$b#It seems you've tried your best... that's all I can ask for. I'm proud of you.#$b#I must return to the other world, now... but feel free to call on me again when you're ready. / 从我们上次谈过之后，你把这个地方好好的改建了一番啊，干的真漂亮。#$b# 看来你是尽了最大努力……我为你感到骄傲。#$b#现在我必须回到另一个世界去了……如果你准备好了随时都可以再联系我。",
        "Auto": "Auto / Auto",
        "NPC.cs.4500": "You could have cleaned up in here a little while I was gone...$a#$e#It's not very nice to have to wade through a bunch of junk after a hard day's work.$a / 我走后你可以稍稍清理一下这里……$a#$e#在辛苦工作了一天之后还得在垃圾堆中穿梭，这实在是太逊了。$a",
        "ChatPadOrange": "ChatPadOrange / ChatPadOrange",
        "Event.cs.1515": "Eggs: {0} / 鸡蛋：{0}",
        "OptionsPage.cs.11245": "Footstep Volume / 脚步音量",
        "NPC.cs.4154": "If you want {0} to dislike you, give her '{1}'. She hates that stuff with a passion. / 如果你想{0}讨厌你，送给她“{1}”。她超恨这些东西。",
        "Utility.cs.5742": "Summer (The Sun Can Bend An Orange Sky) / 夏季（霞光漫天）",
        "ToolReady": "Your {0} is ready. / 你的{0}已经完成了。",
        "GameLocation.cs.8525": "Come back when Pierre's tending the shop. / 等到皮埃尔经营店铺的时候再回来。",
        "Wallpaper.cs.13205": "Decorates the floor of one room. / 装饰一间房间的地板。",
        "Tilde": "Tilde / 波浪号",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13457": "indigestion / 消化不良",
        "Slingshot.cs.14258": "Right-Click to retrieve {0} / 点击右键取回{0}",
        "ShopMenu.cs.11508": "*sigh*... When the door opened I thought it might be Lewis. / *叹气* ……门打开的时候我还以为开门的人是刘易斯呢。",
        "AbigailGame.cs.11898": "Hey! We did it! / 嘿！我们成功了！",
        "Game1.cs.2156": "The Alfalfas / 苜蓿人",
        "ShopMenu.cs.11519": "Welcome to the adventurer's guild. / 欢迎来到探险家公会。",
        "HorseFlute_NoClearance": "Not enough room to summon horse. / 此处空间不够，无法召唤马。",
        "Event.cs.1220": "Mushrooms / 蘑菇",
        "Event.cs.1659": "Selling Star Tokens for just 50g a piece! / 卖星星币啦！50 金一个！",
        "HUDMessage.cs.3824": "New Achievement:  / 新成就：",
        "Utility.cs.5677": "First Night / 第一夜",
        "MeleeWeapon.cs.14122": "The prismatic shard changes shape before your very eyes! This power is tremendous. / 五彩碎片在你眼前改变了形状！真是惊人的能量。^^     You've found the =Galaxy Sword=  ^ / ^你已经找到了=银河之剑=  ^",
        "NPC.cs.4518": "Dear / 亲爱的",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13347": "listening to the new '{0}' record / 听新的“{0}”录音",
        "Utility.cs.5794": "Sam's Band (heavy) / 山姆乐队（重金属）",
        "MediaNextTrack": "MediaNextTrack / 下一个媒体音轨",
        "SocialPage_Relationship_Housemate_Male": "(housemate) / （室友）",
        "Utility.cs.5853": "Journey Of The Prairie King (Undead) / 普瑞尔国王的旅程（亡灵）",
        "TV.cs.13148": "Just kidding... I'm not ready. I don't have anything for you today. / 嘿嘿，开玩笑的……我还没准备好。我今天没什么要教你的。",
        "NPC.cs.4406": "I just feel like sleeping today.$a / 我今天只想睡觉。$a",
        "Event.cs.1318": "I'm so proud of you, my boy! / 我为你感到无比骄傲，我的孩子！^I'm so proud of you, my dear!#$b#You're a better farmer than I ever was, and you've brought great honor to the family name.#$b#I can feel it now... My spirit is finally put to rest. Bless you. / 我为你感到无比骄傲，我亲爱的！#$b#自从我们上次谈话后，你真的把这里变了个样！你比我更适合做一个农夫，这是祖上的荣耀。#$b#我现在能感觉到了……我的灵魂终于可以安息了，祝福你。",
        "ShippingMenu.cs.11392": "Mining / 采矿",
        "Event.cs.1018": "Maybe I was being a little presumptuous earlier... sorry.$5 / 之前是我太冒昧了……对不起。$5",
        "End": "End / End 键",
        "Divide": "Divide / 除号",
        "NPC.cs.4444": "{0}, we're going to have a baby soon.$l / {0}，我们很快就要有孩子了。$l",
        "ResourceCollectionQuest.cs.13673": "#$b#...And here's your payment, as promised. / #$b#……这是你的报酬，我们说好的。",
        "MapPage.cs.11100": "Open 2:00PM to 2:00AM / 营业时间为下午 2:00 至凌晨 2:00",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13512": "hip / 臀部",
        "Game1.cs.3094": "Your mind is filled with thoughts of  / 你脑中充满了各种想法，是关于",
        "NPC.cs.4083": "Did you know that {0} / 你是否知道……{0}",
        "MilkPail.cs.14175": "{0} doesn't produce milk. / {0}不产奶。",
        "TV.cs.13193": "The spirits are somewhat annoyed today. Luck will not be on your side. / 今天精灵们十分气恼。你要走霉运了。",
        "junimokart_slimemusic": "Junimo Kart (Slomp's Stomp) / 祝尼魔赛车（巨怪压顶）",
        "Dialogue.cs.711": "Raincoat / 雨衣",
        "FishingQuest.cs.13248": "Trying to keep the art o' fishing alive... I'll pay {0}g to any ${fisherman^fishing enthusiast}$ who catches {1} {2}. Good luck!  -Willy / 我想努力保存捕鱼的艺术……我可以付{0}金给${任何可以^任何}$捕到{1}{2}${的渔夫^的钓鱼爱好者}$。祝你们好运！——威利",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13449": "the common cold / 普通感冒",
        "TV.cs.13164": "Um... that's odd. My information sheet just says 'null'. This is embarrassing...  / 嗯……奇怪啊。我的信息表显示为“空”。真尴尬……",
        "FarmComputer_Intro_NamedLocation": "{0} Analysis: / {0}的报告：",
        "AbigailGame.cs.11901": "Urghh... / 呃呃……",
        "MiniObelisk_NeedsSpace": "The warp point is obstructed. / 传送点受阻。",
        "NPC.cs.3985": "So...I heard you secretly gave {0} a gift today...$s#$e#Do I have to be suspicious of you?$s#$e#...$a / 那个……我听说你今天偷偷的给{0}送了一件礼物……$s#$e#我还可以信任你吗？$s#$e#……$a",
        "MapPage.cs.11122": "Lonely Stone / 孤独的石头",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13587": "Oh, that's exactly what I need to power my latest invention, @!#$b#Thank you!$h / 噢，那正是我需要的，能作为我最新发明的动力，@！#$b#谢谢！$h",
        "DesertTrader3": "Your coin has no value where I come from... Do you have anything else to trade? / 你的硬币在我的故乡没有任何价值……你还有什么可以交易的吗？",
        "OptionsPage.cs.11236": "Show Merchant Portraits / 显示商人头像",
        "QuestLog.cs.11364": "Cancel Quest / 取消任务",
        "Buff.cs.507": " Speed /  速度",
        "TV.cs.13170": "in Pelican Town / 在鹈鹕镇",
        "Dialogue.cs.742": "far, far away from / 相距甚远",
        "GrandpaStory.cs.12034": "There will come a day when you feel crushed by the burden of modern life... / 有一天你会感到自己被现代生活的重担所压垮……",
        "Dialogue.cs.736": "near / 在附近",
        "Slingshot.cs.14256": "Right-Click to arm {0} with {1} / 右键点击，给{0}装备上{1}",
        "StrengthGame.cs.11669": "Iron / 铁",
        "Utility.cs.5722": "Spring (Wild Horseradish Jam) / 春季（野生辣根酱）",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13487": " I love them. /  我爱他们。",
        "Dialogue.cs.733": "cracked / 破裂",
        "StrengthGame.cs.11662": "Gorilla / 大猩猩",
        "MapPage.cs.11094": "Carpenter's Shop / 木匠的商店",
        "VolumeMute": "VolumeMute / 静音",
        "SlayMonsterQuest.cs.13750": "Hey, I see you culled the {0} population a bit. They've been multiplying quicker than normal due to human activity in the caves, so I'm hoping our efforts prevent them from threatening any other species.#$b#The local wildlife thanks you for what you did today, @. Enjoy your reward.$h / 看来你杀掉了一些{0}。由于人类在山洞活动，它们比正常情况下繁殖的更快，所以我希望我们的努力能够防止它们威胁其他物种。#$b#当地野生动物感谢你今天做的一切，@。享受你应得的酬劳吧。$h",
        "NPC.cs.4429": "*sigh*... my hair looks horrible today.$s#$b#It does... I can tell by the way you're looking at me.$a / *唉*……今天我的发型实在太糟了。$s#$b#真是的……我能从你看我的眼神中看出来。$a",
        "Dialogue.cs.708": "Quail / 鹌鹑",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13357": "serve at breakfast tomorrow / 用于明天的早餐",
        "VolumeDown": "VolumeDown / 降低音量",
        "SocializeQuest.cs.13791": "\n\n- Everyone will like you a little more / \n\n— 大家都会更喜欢你",
        "MeleeWeapon.cs.14142": "+{0} Crit. Chance / +{0} 暴击率",
        "DesertTrader4_male": "The camel seems to like you, sir. That is indeed a very good sign. / 骆驼好像很喜欢你，先生。这真是吉兆。",
        "Utility.cs.5863": "Joja Office Ambience / Joja 办公气氛",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13378": "Feeling gloomy... {0} might cheer me up.\n     -Sebastian / 感觉有些抑郁。也许{0}能让我振作起来。\n     -塞巴斯蒂安",
        "Dialogue.cs.681": "Chalky / 白垩色的",
        "Dialogue.cs.684": "Chunky / 厚实的",
        "Event.cs.1843": "Interesting... I see you and {0} working together on a farm. You seem very pleased about something. / 有意思……我看见你和{0}在一个农场上一起工作。你看上去似乎因为某件事而感到很开心。",
        "TV.cs.13133": "Welcome back to 'Welwick's Oracle'... If you seek hidden knowledge of the future, well you've come to the right place. / 欢迎回到“维尔维克预言”……如果你想知道未来的秘密，那么你来对地方了。",
        "Utility.cs.5864_4": "Song Of Feathers / 羽毛之歌",
        "OptionsPage.cs.11283": "Move Up / 上移",
        "MeleeWeapon.cs.14136": "+{0} Reach / +{0} 可及范围",
        "Event.cs.1797": "Snooch / 斯诺奇",
        "ShippingMenu.cs.11393": "Other / 其它",
        "Event.cs.1531": "$q -1 null#What do you think... should I launch the boat now? / 你觉得呢……现在我应该开船吗？#$r -1 0 yes#Yes. / 是。#$r -1 0 no#Not yet. / 还不用。",
        "NPC.cs.4118": " I gave it to him one year and he wouldn't stop talking about it. /  有一年我把这个送给了他，然后他一直赞不绝口。",
        "GrandpaStory.cs.12040": "Now, let Grandpa rest... / 现在，爷爷要休息了……",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13532": " You brought me the item I asked for! /  你带来了我想要的东西！",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13473": "Hello, it's Emily. I'd like to buy {0} from someone, to craft into some fine jewelry. Thanks! / 你好，我是艾米丽。我想买{0}，来装饰我的精致珠宝。谢谢！",
        "ShopMenu.cs.11486": "Looking to buy something? / 想要买些什么？",
        "MovieTheaterConcessions3": "It's an upgrade from my last job... / 这是我从上份工作学到的经验……",
        "OptionsPage.cs.11288": "Run / 跑动",
        "Utility.cs.5819": "Stardew Valley Overture / 星露谷酒液序曲",
        "DiaryEvent.cs.6669": "...I like him more than just a friend. / ……我很喜欢他，在我眼中，他比朋友更重要。",
        "OptionsPage.cs.11241": "Sound: / 声音：",
        "TutorialMenu.cs.11805": "Crop Basics / 基础作物",
        "Utility.cs.5784": "Starshoot / 射星",
        "Dialogue.cs.794": "the second baby / 第二个婴儿",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13494": "I need {0}, if it's not too inconvenient.  / 我需要{0}。如果方便的话。 ",
        "Dialogue.cs.689": "Lanky / 瘦长的",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13615": "That's not enough... I need {0} of them. / 这些不够啊……我需要 {0} 个。",
        "FarmComputer_TotalForage": "Forage Items: {0} / 采集道具数：{0}",
        "NPC.cs.3961": "...I didn't know. Uh... Sorry. No.$s / ……我不知道。啊……抱歉。不。$s",
        "Game1.cs.2898": "I'm not thirsty right now... / 我现在不渴了……",
        "StrengthGame.cs.11667": "Mountain Troll / 山妖",
        "Event.cs.1666": "Play the slingshot game and win star tokens! / 来玩弹弓游戏吧，赢家可获得星星币！",
        "NPC.cs.4425": "Life sure is different since we got married...$s / 自从我们结婚后生活大不相同了……$s",
        "Event.cs.1837": "Hmmm... now what's this young man's name? ... I believe it starts with an '{0}'. / 嗯嗯……那么这位年青男士叫什么名字呢？……他的名字应该是以“{0}”开头的。",
        "Event.cs.1798": "No? Okay... I'll find a different home for the poor thing.$s / 不要？好的……我会给这可怜家伙找个好归宿的。$s",
        "MapPage.cs.11117": "Community Center / 社区中心",
        "Farmer.cs.2022": "Granger / 农场管家",
        "NPC.cs.4423": "Huh? Nothing's wrong... I'm fine.$s / 哈？什么事也没有……我很好。$s",
        "Utility.cs.5800": "Band Practice / 乐队练习",
        "Farmer.cs.2016": "Farm King / 农场之王",
        "DayTimeMoneyBox.cs.10371": "pm / 下午",
        "OptionsPage.cs.11253": "Lock Toolbar / 锁定工具栏",
        "Utility.cs.5847": "Mines (Crystal Bells) / 矿井（水晶钟）",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13451": "gout / 痛风",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13393": "burrito / 玉米煎饼",
        "Dialogue.cs.757": "Chestervale / 芊桦园",
        "Dialogue.cs.713": "Castle / 城堡",
        "WheelSpinGame.cs.11830": "You Lose / 你输了",
        "NPC.cs.3971": "Heh. Funny joke. / 呵呵。有趣的玩笑。",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13536": " So you saw the ad I posted? /  这么说你看到了我邮寄的广告？",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13367": "Need {0} for my compost pile. Thanks. / 需要{0}加入我的化肥堆。谢谢。",
        "ShopMenu.cs.11525": "I've got just what you need. / 我这里有你需要的东西。",
        "TitleMenu.cs.11734": "You've started the game 10,000 times! I'm impressed. -Ape / 你已经玩了 10,000 次。我很震撼。——Ape",
        "Object.cs.12859": "Decor / 装饰",
        "NPC.cs.4072": "Hi. / 嗨。",
        "Dialogue.cs.804": "/bubblegum/pink / 泡泡粉",
        "GameLocation.cs.8214": "Unop dunyuu doo pusutn snaus / 哝好咕噜噜啊呜哇哟咚^Op hanp o toeday na doo smol^Vhu lonozol yenn huot olait tol / 哝好咕噜噜啊呜哇哟咚",
        "NPC.cs.4172": " Just the thought of it can make him depressed. /  只要想到那东西就能让他萎靡不振。",
        "RandomSentence.7": "The Greasy Hyena stood too close to the other Hyena / 油腻的鬣狗与其他猎狗站的很近",
        "ShopMenu.cs.11461": "I have a rotating selection of hand-made furniture. / 我有许多手工制作的家具可供选择。",
        "Buff.cs.474": "Oil of Garlic / 蒜油",
        "Event.cs.1309": "I'm so proud of you, my boy! / 我为你感到无比骄傲，我的孩子！^I'm so proud of you, my dear!#$b#You've really turned the place around since we last spoke!#$b#You're a better farmer than I ever was, and you've brought great honor to the family name.#$b#I can feel it now... My spirit is finally put to rest. Bless you. / 我为你感到无比骄傲，我亲爱的！#$b#自从我们上次谈话后，你真的让这里变了个样！#$b#你比我更适合做一个农夫，这是祖上的荣耀。#$b#我现在都能感觉到了……我的灵魂终于可以安息了，祝福你。",
        "MediaStop": "MediaStop / 媒体停止",
        "PIRATE_THEME_MUFFLED": "Pirate Theme (Muffled) / 海盗主题曲（低沉）",
        "Event.cs.1647": "Green / 绿色",
        "SlayMonsterQuest.cs.13770": "{0}/{1} {2} defeated / {0}/{1} {2} 已击败",
        "NPC.cs.4446": "I just feel like sleeping today. Don't worry about it.$a / 我今天只想睡觉。你不用担心。$a",
        "MapPage.cs.11177": "Mountain Lake / 山湖",
        "FishingQuest.cs.13260": "One time I caught one the size of a{0} / 有一次我抓住了一条，其体型就如同{0}一样大",
        "TV_Fishing_Channel_Ocean": "ocean / 海洋",
        "Event.cs.1820": "Ahh... Indeed. I see you in a room, having a conversation with a man. / 啊……的确。我看到你在一个房间中和一位男士交谈。",
        "Furniture.cs.12632": "Furniture can't be placed here / 家具不能放在这里",
        "SlayMonsterQuest.cs.13764": "Wanted: Monster hunter to slay {0} {1}s in the local mines. / 追缉令：希望能有怪物猎人清理掉当地矿井里的 {0} {1}。",
        "Utility.cs.5734": "Winter (The Wind Can Be Still) / 冬季（风声依旧）",
        "ShippingMenu.cs.11389": "Farming / 耕种",
        "NPC.cs.4071": "Hi, {0} / 你好，{0}",
        "ShopMenu.cs.11470": "I've got lumps of raw metal for sale. Knock yourself out. / 我有一堆的原材料要出售。请随便挑。",
        "Nauseous_BuffDescription": "Urgh... You're too sick to eat anything / 呃……你非常难受，什么都吃不下",
        "BrowserRefresh": "BrowserRefresh / 浏览器刷新",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13448": "swollen tongues / 舌头发肿",
        "Object.cs.13060": "Too close to another tree. / 太靠近其他树。",
        "SkillsPage.cs.11587": "Dwarvish Translation Guide / 矮人语翻译教程",
        "Dialogue.cs.702": "Robot / 机器人",
        "Farmer.cs.2029": "Cowpoke / 牛仔",
        "TV.cs.13130": "Ah... I sense that a new viewer has joined us. A young lady from... Stardew Valley? Welcome, welcome! / 啊……我感觉到一个新观众加入了我们。一个从……星露谷来的年轻姑娘？欢迎，欢迎！",
        "SkillsPage.cs.11608": "Combat / 战斗",
