        "SaveGame.cs.4698": "Loading Player... / 正在加载播放器……",
        "StrengthGame.cs.11668": "Bodybuilder / 健美运动者",
        "MovieTheaterBoxOffice": "Get your movie tickets right here! Give one to a friend to invite them to the show! / 在这里买电影票！送一张给朋友，邀请他们一起来看！",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13299": "Looking for / 寻找",
        "Tool.cs.14307": "Tool / 工具",
        "StrengthGame.cs.11664": "Ox / 牛",
        "StrengthGame.cs.11660": "HA! Now that's what I like to see! Here, have a star token. / 哈！这才是我想看的！给，拿着这个星星币。",
