        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13540": " It looks perfect. /  看起来很完美。",
        "Tool.cs.14317": "Thanks. I'll get started on this as soon as I can. It should be ready in a couple days. / 谢谢。我会尽快开始的。只需要几天就能准备好。",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13317": "Howdy neighbors! My goats are really hankerin' for {0}. I can't find any myself! Help?     -Marnie / 好心的邻居们！我的山羊真的好想吃{0}。我自己找不到啊！能帮帮我吗？－玛妮",
        "SunRoom": "Alone With Relaxing Tea / 独自休息，享用清茶",
        "Event.cs.1527": "$q -1 null#Should we move forward with the Luau? The governor seems a little hungry. / 我们应该去宴会吗？州长看起来有些饿了。#$r -1 0 yes#Yes, let's start. / 是的，让我们开始吧。#$r -1 0 no#Not yet. / 还没有。",
        "NPC.cs.4062": "Hello! / 你好！",
        "Stats.cs.5129": "Monster Slayer Goal Complete! See Gil for your reward. / 杀怪目标完成！去找吉尔领取你的奖励。",
