        "ShopMenu.cs.11460": "Need some construction supplies? Or are you looking to re-decorate? / 需要一些建筑材料？还是要重新装修？",
        "Event.cs.1632": "Of course I'll dance with you!$h / 当然，我同意与你跳舞！$h",
