        "Game1.cs.2639": "at the beach. / 在沙滩上。",
        "FishingQuest.cs.13277": "Talk to {0} / 与{0}交谈",
        "TV.cs.13124": "Welcome to \"Livin' Off The Land\". We're back again with another tip for y'all. Now listen up: / 欢迎来到“离地而居”。我们回来为你们提供另一个小贴士。请听：",
