        "Darkness_BuffName": "Darkness / 黑暗",
        "ShopMenu.cs.11497": "Rare Goods / 稀有的货物",
        "NPC.cs.4447": "{0}, we're going to have a baby soon.$l / {0}，我们很快就要有孩子了。$l",
        "TitleMenu.cs.11720": "Tip: Shift-click to purchase 5 items at a time. / 小贴士：按住 Shift 再点击鼠标左键就可以一次购买 5 个物品。",
