        "Utility.cs.5855": "Journey Of The Prairie King (Boss) / 普瑞尔国王的旅程（工头）",
        "Utility.cs.5375": "@... %spouse... #$b# As the mayor of Pelican Town, and regional bearer of the matrimonial seal, I now pronounce you wife and... well, wife!$h / @……%spouse……#$b#作为鹈鹕镇的镇长，以及本区婚姻负责人，我现在宣布你们成为彼此的伴侣！$h",
        "NPC.cs.4066": "{0}! / {0}！",
        "VolcanoShop2": "I haven't seen a human here for many years... / 我已经很多年没在这里见到过人类了……",
        "Game1.cs.3045": "Wed / 星期三",
        "Down": "Down / 向下键",
        "Event.cs.1691": "Ah, yes... my crystal ball is swirling with visions of your future, young one. / 啊，是的……我的水晶球正在显示出你的未来，年轻人。",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13308": "I would be so happy if someone delivered one to me. / 如果有人送一个给我，我会很高兴。",
        "NPC.cs.3980": "...!!! $l#$b#I accept!! $h#$b#...$l#$b#I'll set everything up. We'll have the ceremony in 3 days, okay?$h / ……！！！ $l#$b#我接受！！ $h#$b#……$l#$b#我会准备好一切。我们 3 天后举办典礼，如何？$h",
        "Language.1": "English / 英语",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13339": "bring to my evening book club / 带到我的黄昏读书俱乐部",
        "VolcanoShop3": "You are very brave to come here. Please, peruse my stock. / 能够到达此处，你很勇敢。请仔细看看我的存货吧。",
        "Utility.cs.5810": "Mines (Magical Shoes) / 矿井（神奇的鞋）",
        "ShopMenu.cs.11494": "Hiyo, poke. Did you bring coins? Gud. Me sell hats. / 嗨哟，波克。你带金闭了吗？吼。窝卖帽子。",
        "TV.cs.13198": "The spirits are very happy today! They will do their best to shower everyone with good fortune. / 精灵们今天非常开心！他们会尽可能给所有人带来好运的。",
        "OptionsPage.cs.11284": "Move Left / 左移",
        "Event.cs.1714": "Out of Stock. / 没货了。",
        "MapPage.cs.11082": "Open 9:00AM to 4:00PM / 上午 9:00 至下午 4:00 开放",
        "Object.cs.12867": "Monster Loot / 怪物战利品",
        "ResourceCollectionQuest.cs.13655": "You brought the ores I requested.  / 你带来了我需要的矿石。 ",
        "FishingQuest.cs.13262": " folding chair! / 折叠椅",
        "NPC.cs.4508": "Love / 爱",
        "ShopMenu.cs.magicBoat": "...E...Each day... S...Something new... / ……每……每天……都有新……新东西……",
        "OptionsPage.cs.11298": "Inventory Slot #10 / 物品栏格 ＃10",
        "Quest_FinalDay": "Final Day / 最后一天",
        "Dialogue.cs.712": "Shoe / 鞋",
        "Event.cs.1058": "I seem to have lost {0}g / 我好像丢失了 {0} 金",
        "BrowserFavorites": "BrowserFavorites / 浏览器收藏夹",
        "Event.cs.1832": "Ooo... It's dark, and I see you and a certain young man. He looks quite hopeful, and eager to spend time with you. / 噢……太暗了，我看见你和一个年轻男人在一起。他看上去充满期待，但很渴望与你共度时光。",
        "Game1.cs.2157": "Blue Tower / 《蓝塔》",
        "Object.cs.12866": "Flower / 花",
        "FishingGame.cs.12013": "Reward: {0} Star Tokens / 奖励：{0} 星星币",
        "StrengthGame.cs.11703": "Strength Level: {0} / 力量等级：{0}",
        "MovieTheater_Hours": "(Open 9:00AM to 9:00PM) / (营业时间：上午 9:00 至晚上 9:00)",
        "TitleMenu.cs.11724": "The traveling merchant visits Stardew Valley twice a week. She sells a wide variety of goods, often at exorbitant prices! / 巡游商人每周会来星露谷一趟。她几乎什么都卖，就是价格往往有些高！",
        "Dialogue.cs.704": "Pepper / 胡椒",
        "NPC.cs.3926": "Be patient, I still have a lot of work to do. / 稍安勿躁，我这里还有很多事情需要处理。",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13593": "I want to pull a prank on my Dad. I'll need {0}. Keep it secret :)      -Abigail / 我想整蛊一下爸爸。我需要{0}。要保密哦 :) ——阿比盖尔",
        "Buff.cs.501": " Defense /  防御",
        "Dialogue.cs.754": "Zuzu City / 祖祖城",
        "TV.cs.13197": "The spirits are joyous! Someone gave them a nice offering today, and they are very pleased. / 精灵们很高兴！今天有人给了他们很好的祭品，他们非常高兴。",
        "Farmer.cs.1996": "Combat / 战斗",
        "StrengthGame.cs.11705": "Wow. Zero strength. I'm actually impressed with how weak you are. Here's a star token. / 喔，你的力量竟然为 0，你的软弱无能真是让我刮目相看，来，给你个星星币。",
        "IslandTrader4_male": "Please trade wiz me, brother... / 请跟我做个生意，兄弟……",
        "NPC.cs.4138": " hates '{0}'? She finds it absolutely {1}. /  讨厌“{0}”？她觉得那很{1}。",
        "TitleMenu.cs.11719": "Tip: Giving gifts is a good way to make friends with the residents of Stardew Valley. / 小贴士：送礼是与星露谷居民交朋友的好方法。",
        "Seasoning_UsedLast": "You've used up all of your Qi Seasoning. / 你的齐氏调味料已经用完了。",
        "Utility.cs.5683": "Winter / 冬季",
        "IslandTrader3": "Cheap! Cheap! / 超值！超值！",
        "NPC.cs.3965": "You just got engaged! What are you thinking?$s / 你刚刚订婚了！你现在在想什么？$s",
        "ShopMenu.cs.11518": "In the market for a new sword? / 你想要挑选一把新剑吗？",
        "Object.cs.12873": "Progress Mode / 关卡模式",
        "Language.2": "German / 德语",
        "TV.cs.13127": "Greetings! It is I, the queen of sauce... here to teach you a new mouth-watering recipe from my secret cookbook. This week's dish... / 你好啊！是我，酱料女皇……在此向你们传授我的烹饪秘籍中令人垂涎三尺的秘密配方。这周的菜肴是……",
        "Event.cs.1788": "Select a gift for {0}. / 选择一个礼物送给{0}",
        "FishingQuest.cs.13228": "The local {0} population is starting to threaten other species. If you can fish {1} of them for me, it would be a big help.   -Demetrius / 当地的{0}已经开始威胁到其他物种了。如果你能钓些{1}给我，那就再好不过了。——德米特里厄斯",
        "MapPage.cs.11098": "Mines / 矿井",
        "SlayMonsterQuest.cs.13734": "I can remember {0} after I got {1} slime all over my brand new {2} pants... $h#$b# Well, anyways... enjoy your reward. / 我还记得{0}，当{1}的黏液沾满我的新{2}裤子的时候……$h#$b# 算了，不说了……这是给你的报酬。",
        "IslandTrader2": "Coin? No thanks... Trade! / 硬币？那就算了……做生意！",
        "SocializeQuest.cs.13785": "Saying 'Hello' / 打招呼",
        "NPC.cs.3955": "You can't date {0} / 你不能与{0}约会。",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13523": "Buying 1 {0} at three times the market value! Please deliver directly into my hands. / 以三倍市价购买{0}！请直接送到我手上。数量：1",
        "Dialogue.cs.691": "Crusty / 暴躁的",
        "OptionsPage.cs.11238": "Hide Tool Hit Location When Moving / 移动时隐藏工具目标位置",
        "Dialogue.cs.801": "/pale/yellow / 惨白黄色",
        "MapPage.cs.11065": "Backwoods / 边远森林",
        "Event.cs.1730": "You!!! Was that some kind of sick prank?! Those are very private!$4#$b#Here, take 750 star tokens and don't tell a soul.$3#$b#Now go clean up your box and bring me my... item... tomorrow.$3 / 你！！！你怎么还有这种恶趣味？！这些可是个人私隐啊！$4#$b#给，这 750 个星星币是你的了，不要告诉任何人哦。$3#$b#现在马上清理你的格子，明天把我的……物品……带来。$3",
        "MapPage.cs.11062": "Calico Desert / 卡利科沙漠",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13580": "Need {0} for my latest project. Help!    -Maru / 我最新的项目需要{0}。帮帮我！－玛鲁",
        "NPC.cs.4125": " It would make a great gift. /  这将成为一件极好的礼物。",
        "MovieTheaterConcessions1": "Need a snack for the movie? / 想买些零食边看电影边吃吗？",
        "SkillsPage.cs.11591": "Skull Key / 头骨钥匙",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13311": "Greetings! Demetrius here. Could someone please bring me {0}?\nI'm studying them as part of my biological research. / 你好啊！这是德米特里厄斯。谁能给我些{0}吗？\n我想把它们作为我生物学研究的一部分。",
        "Farmer.cs.1922": "You received {1} x{0} ! / 你获得了“{1}”x{0}！",
        "TutorialMenu.cs.11811": "Crafting / 制造",
        "HoeDirt.cs.13924": "Out of season. / 过季。",
        "Zoom": "Zoom / 缩放",
        "Buff.cs.462": "Spooked / 受惊的",
        "StrengthGame.cs.11665": "Horse / 马",
        "Event.cs.1535": "$q -1 null#Oh... are you already finished setting up your grange display? / 哦……你已经准备好农庄展览了吗？#$r -1 0 yes#Yes. / 是。#$r -1 0 no#Not yet. / 还没有。",
        "VolcanoShop0": "A human who speaks our language? I'm impressed... / 人类会说我们的语言？你真了不起……",
        "StrengthGame.cs.11687": "Paper Mache / 纸浆制模型",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13341": "eat in front of the TV / 边吃边看电视",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13583": "I need {0} to power my latest invention. It's the ONLY thing that will work!       -Maru / 我需要{0}来作为我最新发明的动力。只有那玩意可以作为动力！－玛鲁",
        "ResourceCollectionQuest.cs.13672": "#$b#These ores look to be of good quality... You can keep them, of course. I just wanted to see how the local geology is doing. / #$b#这些矿石看上去质量不错……你可以收着，我只是想看看当地的地质情况。",
        "SlayMonsterQuest.cs.13744": "Those slimes can be pretty dangerous in groups.#$b#It should be a little easier to go spelunking now, thanks to your efforts. Enjoy your reward! / 如果那些史莱姆成群结队的话可能会很危险。#$b# 因为你的帮助，现在进行洞穴探险比以前简单一些了。这是你的奖励！",
        "Farmer.cs.2027": "Tiller / 农耕人",
        "Utility.cs.5780": "Music Box Song / 音乐盒之歌",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13528": "Hello @! / 您好@！",
        "Game1.cs.3666": "Screenshot mode activated. Press 'F4' to exit. / 截图模式已激活。按“F4”键退出。",
        "Event.cs.1497": "Um, excuse me.#$b#I have a gift for you. I found it last summer when I was playing at the beach. I hope you like it.$h / 嗨，等下。#$b#我有个礼物要给你。是我去年夏天在海滩上玩的时候发现的。希望你喜欢。$h",
        "Darkness_BuffDescription": "Darkness clouds your vision, making it difficult to see / 黑暗笼罩了你的视野，让你难以视物",
        "CalicoJack.cs.11946": "You Lose / 你输了",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13485": "Could someone bring me {0}? / 有人可以给我带个{0}吗？",
        "Wilted_Bouquet_Effect": "You're no longer dating {0}. / 你和{0}不再约会了。",
        "Event.cs.1684": "Please stand at the red arrow. / 请站在红色箭头处。",
        "Event.cs.1849": "The crystal ball has moved on... Now I see you relaxing on the riverbanks, holding a fishing pole. Oh! Looks like something big is on the line! / 水晶球中的景象发生了改变……现在，我看到你正在河岸休闲放松，拿着鱼竿。噢！看来有一条大鱼上钩了！",
