        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13464": "I'd like to put {0} {1}. Please deliver it some time today. / 我想要一个{0}放在{1}。请在今日内发货。",
        "StrengthGame.cs.11674": "Angry Hog / 愤怒的猪",
        "Dialogue.cs.755": "a small island off the coast / 海滨外的小岛",
        "Object.cs.12995": "You found a 'Geode'! The local blacksmith can break it open for you. Who knows what might be hidden inside? / 你发现了一个“晶球”！当地的铁匠可以帮你敲开它。天知道里面有什么？",
