        "NPC.cs.4180": " I guess everyone has their hang-ups. /  我想每个人都有自己的烦恼。",
        "NPC.cs.4080": "my {0} / 我的{0}",
        "SlayMonsterQuest.cs.13742": "twill / 斜纹布",
        "Slots.cs.12118": "Bet100 / 赌注 100",
        "FarmComputer_MachinesReady": "Machines Ready: {0} / 已完成机器：{0}",
        "PurchaseAnimalsMenu.cs.11352": "Adults can be shorn for wool. Sheep who form a close bond with their owners can grow wool faster. A pair of shears is required to harvest the wool. / 成年绵羊身上的羊毛可以剪下来。与主人关系密切的绵羊长毛更快。需要一把剪刀来剪羊毛。",
        "Event.cs.1825": "Hmm... I see you sitting in a plush chair by the fire... you're surrounded by luxury, yet filled with lonely desperation. / 唔……我看到你坐在火堆旁的太师椅上……你身边全是奢侈品，但是你心中却充满了孤独的绝望。",
        "Event.cs.1853": "Now, just keep in mind that the future isn't set in stone! Whatever I've told you today can still be changed, if you set your heart on it. Farewell. / 现在，只需记住未来不是一成不变的！不管我今天跟你说了什么，如果你用心，还是可以改变未来的。永别了。",
        "Utility.cs.5738": "Mines (A Visitor To The Unknown) / 矿井（探索未知的访客）",
        "ShopMenu.cs.11520": "Slay any monsters? I'll buy the loot. / 有没有击败一些怪物？我想收购你的战利品。",
        "QuestLog.cs.11373": "Journal / 日志",
        "Options.cs.4558": "Sound Effects Volume / 声效音量",
        "StrengthGame.cs.11699": "Wet Tissue / 湿纸巾",
        "SocialPage_Relationship_Husband": "(husband) / （丈夫）",
        "ShopMenu.cs.11502": "Let me see... Oh! I've got just what you need: {0}! / 让我看看……噢！我正好有你需要的：{0}！",
        "Event.cs.1826": "...Oh? It seems you'll be leaving more than a few heartbroken... Are you playing games with those who put their trust in you? Hmm...  / ……哦？看来你将会让很多人心碎啊……你是在玩弄那些信任你的人吗？唔……",
        "Dialogue.cs.709": "Cheese / 奶酪",
        "PurchaseAnimalsMenu.cs.11326": "{0}s Can't Live There. / {0}不能住在那里。",
