        "HoeDirt.cs.13916-2": "This spot is already fertilized / 这个地方已经施过肥了",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13373": "Stardew Valley Meals Service is looking for a temporary worker on {0} to deliver {1} to {2}. Compensation upon delivery. / 星露谷餐饮服务在{0}需要一个临时工来将{1}送给{2}。货到付款。",
        "GameLocation.cs.8715": "Error: Not enough money. / 错误：没有足够的钱。",
        "NPC.cs.3981": "You've already given {0} a gift today. / 你今天已经给了{0}一个礼物。",
