        "Debris.cs.628": "Stone / 石头",
        "Utility.cs.5864_8": "Music Box Song / 音乐盒之歌",
        "Event.cs.1763": "Wha... Yoba...? @, don't... don't you know I'm an atheist? Ugh... $7 / 由巴……？@，你不知道我是无神论者吗？呃。$7",
        "Wallpaper.cs.13203": "Flooring / 地板",
        "ItemRecovery_Engaged": "Alright, I'll see if I can find your lost {0} tonight. I'll drop it off in your mailbox tomorrow morning. / 好，我看看今晚能不能找到你丢失的{0}。明天早上我会把它放在你的邮箱里。",
