        "Farmer.cs.2018": "Agriculturist / 农业学家",
        "Dialogue.cs.807": "/aquamarine / 湛蓝",
        "FishingQuest.cs.13268": "#$b#Well, here's your reward. Congratulations.$h / #$b# 这是给你的奖励。恭喜。 $h",
        "Event.cs.1498": "I'm glad you moved here, farmer @!$h / 我很高兴你能来这里定居，农夫！$h",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13604": "Ah, the {0} I requested! And it's a beautiful one, too. Thank you very much, @. / 是我想要的{0}！真是太漂亮了。非常感谢你，@",
        "GrandpaStory.cs.12026": "...and for my very special grandson: / ……给我特别的孙子：",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13421": "pickle / 腌菜",
        "Utility.cs.5814": "Country Shop / 乡村商店",
        "StrengthGame.cs.11679": "Hot Mustard / 辣芥末",
        "OptionsPage.cs.11299": "Inventory Slot #11 / 物品栏格 ＃11",
        "PageUp": "PageUp / Page Up 键",
        "BiteChime_Default": "Default / 默认",
        "OptionsPage.cs.11237": "Always Show Tool Hit Location / 一直显示工具目标位置",
        "Event.cs.1062": "{0} items from my backpack. / 我背包里的 {0} 样物品。",
        "PurchaseAnimalsMenu.cs.11335": "Lives in the coop. / 饲养在鸡舍里。",
        "MapPage.cs.11092": "1 River Road / 1 河间大道",
        "NPC.cs.4152": "If you want {0} to dislike you, give him '{1}'. He hates that stuff with a passion. / 如果你想{0}讨厌你，送给他“{1}”。他超恨这些东西。",
        "Furniture_Outdoors": "Outdoor Furniture / 户外家具",
        "movie_nature": "Exploring Our Vibrant World / 探索我们充满活力的世界",
        "Event.cs.1862": "Abigail! / 阿比盖尔！",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13585": "Oh! Perfect! Now I can continue the project I was working on.$h#$b#Thanks a bunch, @.$h / 噢！太棒了！现在我可以继续这个项目了。$h#$b#太感谢了，@。$h",
        "NPC.cs.4115": " She loves it. /  她喜欢这个。",
        "OptionsPage.cs.11239.console": "Placement Tile Indicator / ",
        "Game1.cs.3332": "{0} days played. / 游戏天数：{0}。",
        "CalicoJack.cs.11952": "No Winner / 没有赢家",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13508": "gums / 牙床",
        "Dialogue.cs.700": "Buffet / 自助餐",
        "FishingGame.cs.12021": "No Reward... Try Harder / 没有奖励……再加把劲",
        "PurchaseAnimalsMenu.cs.11321": "That Building Is Full / 该建筑物已经满了",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13314": "Looking to dissect {0}. Please deliver to Demetrius at 24 Mountain Road. / 我很期待着解剖{0}。请立刻寄到山路 24 号的德米特里厄斯那里。",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13608": "\n- Makes {0} happy / \n－让{0}很开心",
        "MapPage.cs.11069": "Open 9:00AM to 4:00PM most days / 主要在上午 9:00 至下午 4:00 开放",
        "SlayMonsterQuest.cs.13730": "Ah, @! So you helped us with our slime problem? Thank you!$h#$b#I hope you didn't go through too much trouble...  / 啊，@！所以你帮助我们解决了史莱姆的问题？非常感谢！$h#$b#我希望你之前没有遇上太大的麻烦……",
        "FishingQuest.cs.13258": "They're always hiding in the most peculiar places. / 这些鱼经常躲在奇怪的地方。",
        "Dialogue.cs.743": "uncomfortably close to / 近在咫尺",
        "TitleMenu.cs.11722": "Tip: Right-click to use a weapon's special move. / 提示：点击右键来使用武器的特殊招式。",
        "RightShift": "RightShift / 右 Shift",
        "Event.cs.1260": "I finished writing my book! $h#$b#Well, here it is... '%book'. It's about a government land surveyor who visits a tiny, isolated mining community... and discovers some disturbing secrets.$u#$b#I -almost- feel like I should split the profits with you, considering how much help you gave me!$h / 我写完了我的书！ $h#$b#嗯，就是这个……'%book'。讲的是一个政府土地测量师到访一个小型、孤立的采矿社区……并发现了一些令人不安的秘密。$u#$b#想到你给了我那么多帮助，我几乎觉得我应该分些利润给你！$h",
        "ShopMenu.cs.11457": "Have a look at my wares. / 看看我的商品。",
        "MultiplePetBowls_watered": "#$e#I also filled the pets' water bowls. / #$e#我还给宠物们的水碗都装满了水。",
        "NPC.cs.4488": "I ordered this the other day and it just arrived. / 前几天我订购了这个，它刚到。",
        "MineCart.cs.12106": "You beat Junimo Kart!  / 你通关了祝尼魔赛车！ ",
        "CalicoJack.cs.11927": "Stand / 停止",
        "Ring.cs.1": "Ring / 戒指",
        "EnlW": "EnlW / EnlW",
        "Dialogue.cs.705": "Tomb / 墓地",
        "NPC.cs.4281": "Oh, a birthday gift! Thank you./Oh, a birthday gift! Thank you. / 噢，一个生日礼物！谢谢。/噢，一个生日礼物！谢谢。",
        "Farmer.cs.1992": "Mining / 采矿",
        "Execute": "Execute / 执行",
        "IslandMusic": "Ginger Island / 姜岛",
        "ShopMenu.cs.11512": "Can you smell that? It's the {0} / 你闻到了吗？这是{0}",
        "Farmer.cs.1918": "You received 15 Parsnip Seeds! / 你收到了 15 颗防风草种子！^^'Here's a little something to get you started.^-Mayor Lewis' / ^“收下这些，好好努力吧。^——镇长刘易斯”",
        "Dialogue.cs.749": "Basket Town / 篮子镇",
        "Event.cs.1823": "..  Oh! It's {0}. You seem to be close friends. / ……噢！是{0}。你们似乎是亲密的朋友。",
        "Event.cs.1521": "$q -1 null#Do you think everyone's ready for the egg hunt yet? / 你觉得大家都准备好彩蛋大寻宝了吗？#$r -1 0 yes#Yes, let's start. / 是的，让我们开始吧。#$r -1 0 no#Not yet. / 还没有。",
        "TV.cs.13195": "The spirits are somewhat mildly perturbed today. Luck will not be on your side. / 今天精灵们有些烦躁。你要走霉运了。",
        "NPC.cs.4111": " It's her favorite. /  这是她的最爱。",
        "Utility.cs.5839": "Piano Solo / 钢琴独奏",
        "MapPage.cs.11074": "Home of Emily & Haley / 艾米丽和海莉的家",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13327": "...feel like throwing {0} as hard as I can against the mountain face. Please deliver to Sebastian at 24 Mountain Road. / ……感觉就像是将{0}用力扔向山的表面一样。请寄送给山路 24 号的塞巴斯蒂安。",
        "Event.cs.1719": "Select an ingredient to add. / 选择要添加的材料。",
        "OptionsPage.cs.11272": "Show Flash Effects / 显示闪光效果",
        "PurchaseAnimalsMenu.cs.11357": "Name your new animal:  / 给你的新动物取名字：",
        "Dialogue.cs.695": "Courageous / 勇敢的",
        "ShopMenu.cs.11464": "I've got {2} {0} that would look just {1} in your house. / 我有 {2} 个{0}，可以使你的家看上去十分{1}。",
        "Game1.cs.3047": "Fri / 星期五",
        "ShopMenu.cs.11481": "Need some supplies? / 需要什么物资吗？",
        "ShopMenu.cs.11489": "The season's almost over. I'll be changing stock tomorrow. / 这个季节即将结束。明天我会更换库存。",
        "GrandpaStory.cs.12055": "Dear {0}, / 亲爱的{0}，^^If you're reading this, you must be in dire need of a change.^^The same thing happened to me, long ago. I'd lost sight of what mattered most in life... real connections with other people and nature. So I dropped everything and moved to the place I truly belong.^^^I've enclosed the deed to that place... my pride and joy: {1} Farm. It's located in Stardew Valley, on the southern coast. It's the perfect place to start your new life.^^This was my most precious gift of all, and now it's yours. I know you'll honor the family name, my dear. Good luck.^^Love, Grandpa^^P.S. If Lewis is still alive say hi to the old guy for me, will ya? / ^如果你在读这封信，你一定身处困境期待转机。^^很久以前，我也遇到过相同的情况。当时的我对人生中最重要的东西视而不见……那就是人与人之间的联系以及人与自然之间的关系。所以我放弃了一切并来到了真正属于我的地方。^^^我将那块地的契据放在了信封里……那里寄托了我所有的骄傲和愉悦：{1}农场。它坐落在星露谷，在南海岸。它将是你开启新生活的完美之地。^^这是我最珍贵的礼物，现在它是你的了！我知道你会光宗耀祖的，我亲爱的孙女。祝你好运。^^爱你的，祖父^^顺便说一句，如果刘易斯还活着，你就替我向那个老家伙问好吧，好吗？",
        "Object.cs.12927": "I've scared off 1 crow. / 我已经吓走了一只乌鸦。",
        "FishingGame.cs.10444": "Score: {0} / 得分：{0}",
        "Tool.cs.14303": "Level {0} {1} / {0} 级{1}",
        "OptionsPage.cs.11275.console": "Controller Vibration / ",
        "ShopMenu.cs.11492": "Buy something? / 买点什么东西吗？",
        "FishingQuest.cs.13236": "a genetically modified 'super{0}' escaped from a fishery and started multiplying. / 一个被基因转换的“超级{0}”逃离渔场后开始繁殖。",
        "GrandpaStory.cs.12031": "Now, listen close... / 现在，听好了……",
        "Event.cs.1258": "I finished writing my book, and it ended up being a romance novel! ...You told me once that you enjoyed the genre, and, well, I've also been able to draw some inspiration from real life experiences lately. $l#$b#Here it is, '%book'. It's about a train stewardess who falls in love with a traveling architect... but he's secretly engaged to the ticket collector's daughter!#$b#I *almost* feel like I should split the profits with you, considering how much help you gave me!$h / 我写完了我的书，它是一本爱情小说！……你曾告诉过我你喜欢爱情类的小说，而且我最近也从现实生活中吸取了一些灵感。 $l#$b#在这里，'%book'。是关于一位爱上建筑师的火车乘务员……但是他与收票员的女儿秘密订婚了！#$b#想到你给了我那么多帮助，我*几乎*觉得我应该分些利润给你！$h",
        "NPC.cs.4517": "Honey / 甜心",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13336": "serve at my afternoon tea party / 用于我的下午茶聚会",
        "BlueprintsMenu.cs.10002": "Not Enough Resources / 资源不够",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13612": "\n- {0} will be pleased / \n－{0}会很开心",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13398": "Could someone bring me one? / 有人能给我带一份吗？",
        "NPC.cs.4277": "You remembered my birthday! Thank you. This is great.$h / 你记得我的生日！谢谢你。你真是太贴心了。$h",
        "Dialogue.cs.696": "Reasonable / 明理的",
        "MapPage.cs.11096": "Shop open 9:00AM to 5:00PM most days / 主要在上午 9:00 至下午 5:00 开放",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13392": "taco / 墨西哥卷饼",
        "Utility.cs.5792": "Sam's Band (Electronic) / 山姆的乐队（电子）",
        "fall": "fall / 秋季",
        "Wilted_Bouquet_Meaningless": "It wouldn't make sense to give this to {0}. / 把这给{0}没有任何意义。",
        "NPC.cs.4422": "Sometimes I wonder if I'm doing the right thing with my life...$s / 有时候我都怀疑自己是否已经偏离了人生的正确轨道……$s",
        "SocialPage_Relationship_Single_Female": "(single) / （单身）",
        "NPC.cs.4498": "*sigh*... sometimes I miss my old life.$s / *叹气*……有时我会很想念我过去的生活。$s",
        "Furniture.cs.12623": "Can be placed inside your house. / 可以放进你的房子。",
        "ResourceCollectionQuest.cs.13679": "stone / 石头",
        "Play": "Play / 播放",
        "Event.cs.1500": "It's not much, but I hope you like it.$h / 虽然不是很贵重，但希望你能喜欢。$h",
        "Farmer.cs.2019": "Farmer / 农夫",
        "MapPage.cs.11077": "Open 9:00AM to 3:00PM / 上午 9:00 到下午 3:00 开放",
        "Event.cs.1871": "Willy, with 5 big, fresh fish! / 威利，还有 5 条新鲜的大鱼！",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13468": "on a chain / 在链子上",
        "NPC.cs.4275": "A birthday gift? That's very kind of you! I love it.$h / 生日礼物？你真有心！我很喜欢这件礼物。$h",
        "NPC.cs.4445": "{0}, I'm pregnant. Isn't it wonderful?$l / {0}，我怀孕了。是不是很美妙？$l",
        "Utility.cs.5720": "Spring (The Valley Comes Alive) / 春天（山谷再次充满生机）",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13530": " Is that the {0} I requested? /  这是我要的{0}吗？",
        "fieldOfficeTentMusic": "Professor Snail's Radio / 蜗牛教授的收音机",
        "SlayMonsterQuest.cs.13747": "An invasive crab species is living in the local mine, threatening the native wildlife! These creatures are known for disguising themselves as stones. I'll pay someone to slay {0} of them.  -Demetrius / 一种入侵类的蟹生活在当地的矿井，威胁到本地的野生动物！这些蟹会伪装成石头。如果有人能杀掉 {0} 只入侵蟹的话，我会给他奖励的。——德米特里厄斯",
        "QuestionEvent.cs.6692": "Choose a name: / 选择一个名字：",
        "MustBePlacedInBarn": "Must be placed in a barn. / 只能放置在谷仓里。",
