        "LeftWindows": "LeftWindows / 左 Windows",
        "Game1.cs.2634": "near Marnie's ranch. / 玛妮的农场附近。",
        "Utility.cs.5758": "Cloud Country / 多云的乡村",
        "NPC.cs.4427": "*sigh*... my skin looks horrible today.$s#$b#It does... I can tell by the way you're looking at me.$a / ＊叹气＊……今天我的皮肤真是糟透了。$s#$b#真是……从你看我的眼神我就知道了。$a",
