        "ShopMenu.cs.11487": "Got anything you want to sell? / 有想要出售的东西吗？",
        "NPC.cs.4120": " I gave it to her one year and she wouldn't stop talking about it. /  有一年我把这个送给了她，然后她一直赞不绝口。",
        "MapPage.cs.11172": "Stardrop Saloon / 星之果实酒吧",
        "ResourceClump.cs.13964": "It looks pretty solid... maybe a very strong pickaxe could break it? / 看起来很坚固……也许需要非常强大的十字镐才能敲开它？",
