        "Dialogue.cs.734": "melted / 融化",
        "AbigailGame.cs.11902": "Nooo! / 不！",
        "NPC.cs.4474": "I got up early and fed all the farm animals. I hope that makes your job a little easier today. / 我早早地就起床把农场的牲口都喂了一遍。希望能减轻一点你工作上的压力。",
        "Buff.cs.472": "Adrenaline Rush / 肾上腺冲击",
        "Game1.cs.3097": "You feel an unwavering connection to the valley itself. / 你感受到自己与星露谷之间那坚不可摧的联系。",
        "NPC.cs.4274": "You remembered my birthday? I'm impressed. Thanks.$h / 你记得我的生日？我真是受宠若惊啊，谢谢。$h",
        "RandomSentence.2": "The Gooey Buffet spoke atop the Castle / 粘稠的自助餐在城堡上交谈着",
        "Farmer.cs.2026": "Smallholder / 小农场主",
        "AbigailGame.cs.11897": "Half-way done! / 已经完成一半了！",
