        "TV.cs.13181": "Expect a few inches of snow tomorrow. / 明天的降雪可能会达到几英尺。",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13360": "I woke up thinking about how much I want {0} for dinner.\nCould someone make it for me? / 我醒来后就感觉今晚超级想吃{0}。\n谁能给我做点吗？",
