        "Event.cs.1818": "Hmm... I see you laying on a cot... It looks like a hospital. {0} is there to keep you company while you recover. What a nice friend. / 嗯嗯……我看见你躺在一张小床上……貌似是在医院里。当你在那里休养时，{0}一直陪着你。真是挚友啊。",
