        "PurchaseAnimalsMenu.cs.11354": "Livestock: / 家畜：",
        "SlayMonsterQuest.cs.13725": "Frost Jellies in the frozen depths of the mine. / 矿井深处冻土中的冰冻史莱姆。",
        "Game1.cs.3756": "Mr. Lewis / 刘易斯先生",
