        "Debuff_Weakness": "Weakness / 虚弱",
        "NumLock": "NumLock / NumLock",
        "SlayMonsterQuest.cs.13711": "The monsters known as 'Duggies' are making a mess of the local mine! The holes they create could weaken the structural integrity of the mines. Could someone defeat {0} of these creatures? / 名叫“掘地虫”的怪物把当地的矿井搅得一团糟！它们挖的洞可能会破坏矿山的结构完整性。有人可以打败数量为{0}的这些怪物吗？",
        "MapPage.cs.11089": "Sewer / 下水道",
