        "TV.cs.13172": "on the beach / 在沙滩上",
        "Object.cs.12858": "Fishing Tackle / 钓具",
        "MapPage.cs.11084": "Open 12:00PM To 12:00AM / 下午 12:00 至上午 12:00 开放",
        "MapPage.cs.11174": "Pelican Beach / 棕榈镇海滩",
        "ResourceCollectionQuest.cs.13650": ", for inspection. / ，以备检查。",
        "TV.cs.13107": "Fortune Teller / 算命占卜",
        "MeleeWeapon.cs.14132": "{0} - {1} Damage / {0} - {1} 伤害",
        "PurchaseAnimalsMenu.cs.11337": "Happy adults lay duck eggs every other day. / 快乐的成年鸭子每隔一天都下鸭蛋。",
        "Dialogue.cs.703": "Planet / 行星",
        "TV.cs.13175": "It's going to be clear and sunny tomorrow... perfect weather for the {0}! The event will take place {1}, starting between {2} and {3}. Don't be late! / 明天将是个大晴天……对{0}来说将是完美的天气！活动将在{1}举行，将于 {2} 到 {3} 之间开始。别迟到了！",
        "Utility.cs.5829": "Jaunty / 轻松活泼",
        "SlayMonsterQuest.cs.13732": "squirmers.  / 蠕动的小东西。",
        "NPC.cs.4144": "{0} really hates '{1}'! She told me.$h / {0}非常讨厌“{1}”！她跟我说的。$h",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13548": "The Wizard, M. Rasmodius, wishes to study the arcane properties of the {0}. You will be rewarded. / M·拉斯莫迪斯法师希望了解{0}的神秘特质。事成后你将得到回报。",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13285": "Delivery / 交付",
        "SkillsPage.cs.11607": "Fishing / 钓鱼",
        "NPC.cs.4058": "Hi... / 你好……",
        "NPC.cs.4001": "Honey... I wanted to give you that fruit as a symbol of my love.$l / 亲爱的……我想送你那种水果，作为我对你的爱的象征。$l",
        "NPC.cs.3972": "Oh!! ... $l #$b#@... I'm sorry, but no. I won't marry you right now.$s / 噢！……$l #$b#@……对不起，但不行。我现在不能和你结婚。$s",
        "NPC.cs.4470": "I got up early to water some crops and they were already done! You've really got this place under control.$h / 我起了个大早给作物浇水，并且浇完了！你把这个地方管理得很好。$h",
        "Dialogue.cs.806": "/bright/orange / 亮橙色",
        "TV.cs.13182": "It's going to be a beautiful, sunny day tomorrow! / 明天天气晴朗，风和日丽！",
        "AdoptPet": "Will you adopt this {0}? / 你打算收养这只{0}吗？",
        "Utility.cs.5802": "The Stardrop Saloon / 星之果实酒吧",
        "ItemDeliveryQuest.cs.13337": "pair with a dry red wine this evening / 与今晚的红葡萄酒搭配",
        "ResourceCollectionQuest.cs.13677": "Hey, looks like you got the {0} I asked for.  / 嗨，看来你找到了我要的{0}。 ",
        "ShopMenu.cs.11517": "The caves can be dangerous. Make sure you're prepared. / 洞穴里面可能会很危险。请确保自己已经做好了准备。",
        "Event.cs.1020": "Thanks for helping out in the lab.$h / 谢谢你在实验室的帮忙。$h",
        "NPC.cs.4512": "Peach / 桃子",
        "HoeDirt.cs.13925": "Can't plant here. / 不能种在这里。",
        "Options.cs.4559": "Typing Sound / 打字音",
        "ResourceClump.cs.13952": "Your pickaxe isn't strong enough to break this. / 你的十字镐不够强大，无法敲碎这个。",
        "NPC.cs.4294": "That hurt! What's your problem?$s / 真伤人！你到底在想什么？$s",
        "Game1.cs.2899": "I'm too full... / 我太饱了……",
        "SkillsPage.cs.11605": "Mining / 采矿",
        "ResourceCollectionQuest.cs.13657": "Thank you. / 谢谢。",
        "Event.cs.1831": "Ooo... It's dark, and I see you and a certain young man. He looks a little bashful, but happy to be with you. / 噢……太暗了，我看见你和一个年轻男人在一起。他看上去有点害羞，但很乐意和你在一起。",
