        "Game1.cs.2575": "Gamepad disconnected. / 游戏手柄失去连接。",
        "Event.cs.1584": "Your grange display has been judged. Return to Mayor Lewis for the result! / 你的农庄展览已经评定过了。去镇长刘易斯那里获取结果！",
        "Dialogue.cs.746": "on a different planet from / 在不同的行星上",
        "RandomSentence.12": "The Reasonable Hyena spoke with the Shoe / 有理性的鬣狗与鞋子交谈",
        "Dialogue.cs.701": "Biscuit / 饼干",
        "Event.cs.1761": "...You're right. Jas... Ugh, God... I'm a horrible, *hic*... selfish person.$7#$b#Now I feel even worse...$7 / ……你是对的。贾斯……呃，天哪……我太自私了, *呃呃*……我是自私的人。$7#$b#现在我觉得更内疚了……$7",
        "DayTimeMoneyBox.cs.10370": "am / 上午",
        "Pickaxe.cs.14194": "Your pickaxe isn't strong enough to break this yet. / 你的十字镐不够坚硬，无法敲开它。",
        "Farmer.cs.1972": "the farm / 农场",
        "Event.cs.1850": "The crystal ball has moved on... It's you... in the forest. You spot some rare and delicious mushrooms hidden beneath a clump of grass... what a find! / 水晶球中的景象发生了改变……是你……在森林里。你在草丛下面发现了珍稀美味的蘑菇……捡到宝了！",
        "TV.cs.13153": "You learned how to cook '{0}'! / 你学会了烹饪“{0}”的方法！",
        "TV.cs.13114": "The Queen Of Sauce / 酱料女皇",
        "SpecialItem.cs.13092": "You've found the {0}! You're not sure what it's for, but it seems important. It's been added to your wallet. / 你找到了一把{0}！你不太确定这是做什么用的，但它看上去很重要。它已添加到你的钱包中。",
        "Dialogue.cs.692": "Fantastic / 奇妙的",
        "Utility.cs.5756": "Mines (Cloth) / 矿井（布）",
        "MapPage.cs.11087": "Open 8:00AM to 6:00PM / 上午 8:00 到下午 6:00 开放",
        "Game1.cs.2640": "The {0} has begun  / {0}已开始",
        "Utility.cs.5762": "Grandpa's Theme / 祖父的主题",
        "FishTank_Full": "You cannot add any more items of this type / 无法再添加此类型的物品",
        "EndCredits_SongName": "Stardew Valley Forever / 永远的星露谷",
        "Farmer.cs.2028": "Farmhand / 农场工人",
        "Object.cs.12855": "Seed / 种子",
        "NPC.cs.4192": "...#$e#...#$e#...#$e#It's for members only, kid. Now Scram.#$e#... / ……#$e#……#$e#……#$e#只有会员才能进，孩子。赶紧走吧。#$e#……",
        "SlayMonsterQuest.cs.13752": "The monsters known as {0} are throwing the elemental balance into disarray. I would like an adventurer to enter the mines and slay {1} of these {2}.  -M. Rasmodius, Wizard / 称为{0}的怪物让元素平衡陷入混乱。我想让一位探险家进入矿井，杀掉 {1} 只{2}。——法师 M·拉斯莫迪斯",
