      "Entries": {
        "ScienceHouse.6": "It's locked. / 锁上了。",
        "WitchHut.4": "You uncork the bottle and waft the odor into your nostrils. The odor is surprisingly pleasant, with hints of apricot and spice berry. / 你拔去瓶塞扇了下里面的味道到鼻子里。那气味确是出奇的好闻，像是杏和香辛料的味道。",
        "JojaMart.80": "Joja Multipurpose Detergent -- Use it for your laundry, for your dishes, to clean your hands, as a shampoo, and even as toothpaste! Mix it with JojaMeal to make a delicious icing. / Joja 多用途清洁剂——用来洗衣服、刷盘子、洗手、洗头、甚至刷牙！与 Joja 餐混合可以做出美味的糖霜。",
        "AnimalShop.20": "Why are you looking through my trash can?$s / 你在我的垃圾桶里面找什么？$s",
        "MovieTheater_Mother2": "Woman: How about some apple slices? No? *sigh*... okay... / 妇女：来点苹果脆片怎么样？不要？唉……好吧……",
        "JojaMart.77": "Grape Nibble-Pebbles / 葡萄细咬卵石",
        "MovieTheater_Welwick": "Welwick: Hmm, not many people here... and I invested a lot of money in this movie! / 维尔维克：嗯，来看的人不多啊……我在这部电影上可是投了好多钱！",
        "Pirates7_WinNoPrize": "Come back again any time! / 随时再来！",
        "SeedShop.7": "'Journey Of The Prairie King: Console Edition' / “草原之王的冒险之旅：控制台版本”",
        "Blacksmith.1": "There's a tape inside 'The Essential Blues Collection, vol. 2 / 在‘基本蓝调系列’里有一卷胶带，第 2 卷",
        "JojaMart.68": "Searing pain sauce / 灼伤酱",
        "Town-Halloween.3": "\"Our Beloved Mona\" / “我们亲爱的莫娜”",
        "JojaMart.12": "Granny's sauce / 奶奶的酱汁",
        "WitchHut.2": "It would probably be a bad idea to stick your tender arm in there. / 你最好不要把你那纤细的手臂伸进去。",
        "ScienceHouse.13": "Stereo microscope / 立体显微镜",
        "AnimalShop.18": "Mmm.... microwave pizza. / 嗯……微波比萨饼。",
        "JojaMart.96": "Canned fish... now with teeth whitening sauce. / 鱼罐头……现在配有牙齿美白酱。",
        "JoshHouse.8": "You peek into Alex's drawer. There's clothes, hair gel, and a box of gridball trading cards. / 你偷看了下亚历克斯的抽屉。里面有衣服、发胶以及一个装着格球交易卡的盒子。",
        "JojaMart.17": "JojaDiet -- Low fat beans! In a sweet sugar-sauce / Joja 减肥产品——低脂豆子！蘸香甜糖酱",
        "HaleyHouse.1": "It's locked. / 锁上了。",
        "JojaMart.35": "100% pure honey-flavored 'sauce' / 100% 纯蜂蜜口味“酱”",
        "Town-Fair.4": "Tourist: Wow. That's the biggest cheese wheel I've ever seen. Very impressive. / 游客:哇，这是我见过最大的奶酪。令人印象深刻。",
        "Pirates7_0": "DART MAN: Care for a game o' darts? You've got 20 darts to score exactly 301 points. / 飞镖伙计：来一局飞镖不？你要在 20 镖之内投出 301 分整。",
        "Town.1": "Clinic - Hours 9:00 AM - 3:00 PM / 门诊时间——上午 9:00——下午 3:00",
        "ArchaeologyHouse.8": "The Friendly Little Slime / 友好的小泥",
        "WitchHut.3": "The bone is probably covered in bacteria. You decide not to touch it. / 这骨头上可能布满了细菌。因此你决定不去碰它。",
        "JojaMart.86": "Canned fish... now with teeth whitening sauce. / 鱼罐头……现在配有牙齿美白酱。",
        "JoshHouse.4": "'Dealing With Loss' / “应对挫折”",
        "MovieTheater_ConcessionMan": "Moviegoer: Urgh... Too many snack options! / 观众：呃……有太多零食可以选择了！",
        "Blacksmith.10": "It's full of soot. / 满是烟尘。",
        "Farm_Fishing.1": "Grandpa's Shrine / 爷爷的神龛",
        "AnimalShop.6": "You rummage through Marnie's dresser. It's mostly long dresses, but there's a pair of brown suspenders in here as well. / 你翻找着玛妮的梳妆台，里面大多数是长裙，但这里还有一条吊带裤。",
        "BathHouse_WomensLocker.1": "Items for women. / 女性用品。",
        "Town-Halloween.1": "Clinic - Hours 9:00 AM - 3:00 PM / 门诊时间——上午 9:00——下午 3:00",
        "JojaMart.41": "Protein powder / 蛋白粉",
        "AnimalShop.5": "The little family is gathered around the dinner table. Wait... except Grandpa. He's wedged under the bed for some reason. / 小家庭围坐在餐桌边。等等……除了爷爷。出于某种原因，他挤到了床底下。",
        "MovieTheater_PurpleHairLady": "Woman: Get lost... I'm busy rubbing elbows with the Governor! / 女性：我迷路了……我不停地和州长擦肩而过！",
        "MovieTheater_Morris2": "Ah, it's our very important investment partner! Enjoy the show, and don't forget to buy a bag of JojaCorn on your way in!$h / 啊，我们重要的投资伙伴来了！尽情享受这场演出吧，别忘了在你来的路上买一包 Joja 玉米！$h",
        "JojaMart.97": "Cowboy sauce / 牛仔酱",
        "JojaMart.55": "Powdered cream / 奶油粉",
        "Town-Fair.7": "It's old and faded... / 很古老，而且都褪色了……",
        "FishShop.2": "It's a tackle box. It's full of lures, bobbers, hooks, and fishing line. / 这是一个钓具箱，里面满是鱼饵、浮标、鱼钩和鱼线。",
        "ScienceHouse.2": "For a gadgeteer, Maru's computer is pretty old. She's still backing up her files to floppy disk. / 作为一个小工程师，玛鲁的电脑已经很老旧了。她备份文件时还在使用软盘。",
        "AnimalShop.17": "It's locked. / 锁上了。",
        "JojaMart.109": "Canned meals / 罐头食物",
        "ScienceHouse.7": "It's some kind of device Maru's working on. It looks pretty scrappy. / 这是玛鲁正在制造的某种设备，目前看上去还是支离破碎的样子。",
        "SeedShop.2": "David the Guinea Pig / 大卫 豚鼠",
        "JojaMart.79": "Joja Oil -- A proprietary blend of delicious oils. Use it for any purpose. / Joja 油——一种专有的美味混合油。有多种用途。",
        "SebastianRoom.1": "The radio isn't plugged in. / 收音机电源未接入。",
        "ManorHouse.1": "Mayor's oven could use a good cleaning. / 镇长的炉子应该好好清洗一下了。",
        "JoshHouse.3": "'Pro Gridball Season 44: Stats and Standings' / “职业格球第 44 赛季：统计和排名”",
        "JojaMart.95": "Carbo cones. Tasty little cone-shaped snacks that will fill your stomach bag. / 糖锥。美味的锥形小零食，可以填饱你的胃。",
        "SebastianRoom.2": "Graphic novel / 漫画小说",
        "JojaMart.2": "'Maple Sauce'... It's a lot like syrup! / “枫酱”……更像是枫糖酱！",
        "AnimalShop.12": "It's a mess of arts and crafts. / 这是一大堆艺术品和工艺品。",
        "AnimalShop.13": "It doesn't look used. Maybe it's a collector's ball. / 看起来它没被使用过。也许这是一个收藏家的球。",
        "SeedShop.3": "David the Guinea Pig / 大卫 豚鼠",
        "BathHouse_MensLocker.1": "This locker smells awful. / 这个储物柜味道很难闻。",
        "JojaMart.19": "11-grain bread / 11 种谷粮面包",
        "Town-EggFestival.2": "It's old and faded... / 很古老，而且都褪色了……",
        "JojaMart.5": "Hoisin sauce / 海鲜酱",
        "JojaMart.98": "Vacuum-sealed marinated mushrooms / 真空包装腌制蘑菇",
        "Forest.2": "@ Cindersap Forest / @ 煤矿森林^> Pelican Town / > 鹈鹕镇",
        "JojaMart.76": "Blue Alien ENERGY... Get LAUNCHED / 蓝色外星能量……发射",
        "Blacksmith.2": "You rifle through Clint's personal effects. There's a stack of blacksmith aprons, some magazines, an old sword, and a nice picture of his mother. / 你翻找着克林特的私人用品。有一堆铁匠围裙、几本杂志、一把旧剑和他母亲的漂亮照片。",
        "JojaMart.24": "White bread, fortified with essential nutrients / 白面包，富含基本营养素",
        "Town-Fair.6": "Tourist: It's a fine-looking town you've got here. Nice and cozy, and a real sense of community. / 游客：你们的小镇真是美丽啊。很舒适，是一个真正意义上的社区。",
        "JojaMart.89": "Bread / 面包",
        "ManorHouse.2": "A traditional tea setting. The mayor must be pretty serious about tea. / 一个传统的茶具。镇长一定是品茶的行家。",
        "Town.3": "It's old and faded... / 很古老，而且都褪色了……",
        "ScienceHouse.14": "Stereo microscope. / 立体显微镜。",
        "JojaMart.60": "Powdered breakfast -- Just add water. (Eggs & Potatoes) / 粉状早餐——只需加水。（鸡蛋和土豆）",
        "ArchaeologyHouse.2": "Is War With The Gotoro Empire Necessary? A Unique Perspective by P.W.Kranzhauer / 真的有必要和戈特洛国进行战争吗？由凯安扎尔教授所提供的独特视角",
        "JojaMart.22": "Very Mild Sauce / 非常温和的酱",
        "JoshHouse.6": "It's a thirty pound weight. / 30 磅重。",
        "JojaMart.34": "Mild Sauce / 温和酱汁",
        "JojaMart.18": "Protein shakes / 蛋白奶昔",
        "HarveyRoom.7": "There's a tape inside: 'Anthology Of Classic Jazz' / 里面有一卷磁带：“经典爵士乐精选”",
        "Trailer.3": "'The Solarion Chronicles' / “索拉里昂历代记”",
        "SamHouse.5": "Guitar picks and skateboard wheels. / 吉他拨片和滑板车轮。",
        "JojaMart.88": "Strawberry flavored lollipops / 草莓味棒棒糖",
        "JojaMart.107": "Pasta in a can. / 罐装意大利面。",
        "BathHouse_WomensLocker.3": "It's Abigail's locker. It stinks pretty bad. / 这是阿比盖尔的储物柜。气味相当难闻。",
        "JojaMart.10": "'Maypul' Syrup / “枫露”糖浆",
        "ElliottHouse.5": "It's a mini-palm, imported from Calico Desert. / 这是一个小的棕榈树，从卡利特沙漠那里进口来的。",
        "SeedShop.1": "'11 Solo Sonatas For The Wooden Flute' / “11 独奏奏鸣曲 木笛”",
        "JojaMart.4": "Taco sauce for babies / 婴儿用塔可酱",
        "JojaMart.8": "Sugar-Free Lollipop / 无糖棒棒糖",
        "LeahHouse.6": "No Messages. / 没有留言信息。",
        "JojaMart.67": "Hand soap / 洗手皂",
        "HarveyRoom.4": "It's Harvey's model airplane collection. / 这是哈维的飞机模型收藏。",
        "JojaMart.16": "Pretzel snacks / 椒盐饼干",
        "JojaMart.50": "Sugar cones / 宝塔糖",
        "JojaMart.102": "Individually-sealed pancakes / 单独封装薄煎饼",
        "JoshHouse.10": "It's a gridball. / 这是一个格球。",
        "JojaMart.91": "Laundry Detergent -- now with 10x the fragrance! / 洗衣液——现在有 10 种香味！",
        "SeedShop.4": "'The Enduring Value Of Small Business' / “小型企业的持久价值”",
        "JojaMart.21": "Hair Gel -- X-treme hold / 发胶——长效保持",
        "JojaMart.83": "Disks and pucks of pure gluten. / 圆盘和纯面筋球。",
        "JojaMart.9": "24-grain bread / 24 种谷粮面包",
        "HarveyRoom.10": "You didn't find anything, and now your hands smell bad. / 你什么也没找到，还沾了一手臭味。",
        "Hospital.3": "It's probably not a good idea to stick your hands in there. It's full of used syringes, dirty swabs, and little nozzles that Harvey stuck into people's ears. / 最好别把你的手放到那里面。里面都是用过的注射器、脏药签、还有哈维插到人们耳朵里的医用喷嘴。",
        "HaleyHouse.17": "To our beloved girls: / 致我们心爱的女孩们：^We miss you and hope that you are doing okay on your own. We just left the Fern Islands last night, after staying for two months.^It was a wonderful experience... highly recommended.^Make sure you eat healthy and don't forget to pay the electricity bill!^^Love, Mom & Dad / 我们很想念你们，也希望你们过的很好。我们在芬群岛待了两个月，昨晚刚刚离开。^那是段很奇妙的经历……强烈推荐你们也去那里看看。^一定要健康饮食，还有不要忘记交电费！^^爱你们的爸爸妈妈",
        "ManorHouse.3": "Won't you come by tomorrow night? / 你明晚不来吗？^If you come through the back window no one will notice.^I'd like to see you more often.^I know you're busy but can't you make time for me?^I hope to see you tomorrow.^-M / 你从后窗进来不会有人注意的。^我想多见你几面。^我知道你很忙，但你就不能腾出一些时间陪陪我吗？^我希望明天能见到你。^——M",
        "JojaMart.106": "Vacuum-sealed marinated mushrooms / 真空包装腌制蘑菇",
        "ElliottHouse.4": "It looks like Elliott is trying to grow a bonsai tree. It looks cool so far! / 看起来，艾利欧特打算种植一个盆栽。它看起来酷呆了！",
        "HaleyHouse.13": "'Build Your Own Darkroom From Scratch' / “白手起家建立你自己的暗室”",
        "JojaMart.53": "Silly Sauce / 傻瓜酱",
        "HaleyHouse.18": "'Super Fashion Girl' magazine / 《超级时髦女孩》杂志",
        "JojaMart.23": "Take-home churro kit / 可带回家的油炸饼工具包",
        "BathHouse_WomensLocker.2": "It's Penny's locker. There's a frilly bathing suit inside. / 这是潘妮的储物柜。里面有一个镶褶边的泳衣。",
        "HaleyHouse.6": "There's a little note on the pot. 'Something to remember me by. -Sandy' / 盆里有一张小字条。“看到它你就会想起我。——桑迪”",
        "Town-Fair.2": "Are you strong like me? Smash stone! / 你和我一样强壮吗？那就砸石头吧！",
        "ScienceHouse.10": "Periodic Table / 周期表",
        "JojaMart.105": "Hot sauce / 辣酱",
        "MovieTheater_RedCapGuy": "Man: Uh oh... I think I'm a little overdressed for this place... / 男性：不妙啊……我觉得好像穿得太正式了……",
        "JojaMart.63": "Powdered wine / 粉末状酒精",
        "JojaMart.48": "Dehydrated shrimp snack. / 脱水虾零食。",
        "AnimalShop.10": "It's a Mega Station. There's a game in it, but it's routed through a Code Sultan XL. Looks like someone's been cheating. / 这是一个大数据站。里面有一个游戏，但游戏是通过多代码苏丹 XL 途径建立的。看起来像有人一直在作弊。",
        "AnimalShop.16": "Doesn't seem like Jas uses this much. / 看上去，贾斯并不经常使用这个。",
        "Pirates8": "BARTENDER: Oi guv!... Grog and tasties are fer da pirates only. / 酒保：喂，先生！……这里滴酒菜只卖给海盗。",
        "JojaMart.14": "Double Butter Ranch Chips / 双黄油农场薯条",
        "JoshHouse.12": "'Cookies For Every Season' / “赛季专用饼干”",
        "SeedShop.10": "Spirit Board / 灵板",
        "Saloon.2": "Cooking channel. 24/7 cooking tips, game shows, and restaurant reviews. / 烹饪频道。全天候烹饪秘诀、游戏表演、饭店评估。",
        "Town-Christmas.4": " Archaeology Office - Open 8:00 AM to 6:00 PM /  考古学办公室 - 开放时间上午 8:00 到下午 6:00 ",
        "Trailer.4": "It's full of empty beer bottles. / 里面全是空啤酒瓶。",
        "Farm.1": "Grandpa's Shrine / 爷爷的神龛",
        "AnimalShop.8": "Looks like he's using the radio as an alarm clock. / 看来他把收音机当闹钟在用。",
        "JojaMart.62": "Sugar stars / 糖果星星",
        "Town-Halloween.4": " Archaeology Office - Open 8:00 AM to 6:00 PM /  考古学办公室 - 开放时间上午 8:00 到下午 6:00",
        "MovieTheater_Marlon2": "That was an interesting one... what'd you think, Gil?#$b#...Gil?#$b#...He's out cold. / 这部电影还挺有意思……你觉得呢，吉尔？#$b#……吉尔？#$b#……他没反应了。",
        "JojaMart.45": "Mouthwash / 漱口水",
        "Hospital.4": "Is life sometimes difficult? Do you ever have trouble staying focused? Talk to your doctor about Pravoloxinone. / 是否有时感到生活艰难？你是否曾经遇到过一直解决不掉的烦恼？如果有的话可以到医生那里去取普拉沃罗兴农药剂。^(Pravoloxinone is not for everyone. Side effects may include insomnia, severe anger, uncontrollable swelling of the throat, permanent discoloration of the lips, hair loss, and stroke. In extremely rare cases (1 in 500), test subjects experienced complete disintegration of one or more bones.)  / （普拉沃罗兴农并不见得适合每一个人。副作用可能包括失眠、暴怒、喉咙处出现肿胀、双唇永久变色、脱发、中风。在极少数情况下（1/500）服用对象会有一根骨头或者多跟骨头完全解体。） ",
        "MovieTheater_ConcessionMan2": "Moviegoer: Ah, look at that popcorn go! Oh, the sounds... the smells! / 观众：啊，看那爆米花！哦，这声音……这香气！",
        "BathHouse_MensLocker.3": "You're too weak to lift it. / 你太虚弱了，提不起来的。",
        "MovieTheater_ShortsMan": "Corner Guy: Brr... it's kind of drafty over here... I'm glad I wore my long pants! / 街角小子：哇……这里风有点大……幸好我穿了长裤！",
        "SebastianRoom.3": "'Solarion Chronicles:The Game' / “索拉里昂英雄传奇：游戏”",
        "HarveyRoom.1": "A comparison between fighter planes of the Ferngill Republic and the Gotoro Empire. / 芬吉尔共和国与戈特洛国的战斗机之对比。",
        "ElliottHouse.3": "It's an empty cubby. / 这是一个空柜子。",
        "Trailer.5": "'Fairys, Junimos, and other Fables' / “仙女，祝尼魔和其他寓言”",
        "SamHouse.1": "It's empty. / 它是空的。",
        "MovieTheater_Marcello": "Marcello: What a spread! I think I'll go for the bourbon mayonnaise. Hehe! / 马塞罗：这电影真难看！我觉得我得来点波旁威士忌蛋黄酱。呵呵！",
        "JojaMart.43": "Oat bread / 燕麦面包",
        "Farm_Foraging.1": "Grandpa's Shrine / 爷爷的神龛",
        "Pirates7_Win": "DART MAN: Well, sink me! That's some good throwing! / 飞镖伙计：哇塞，给力！投得很厉害！",
        "HaleyHouse.10": "It's a deluxe vanity. There's all kinds of creams, paints, and powders dotting the surface. / 这是一个豪华的化妆台。有各种各样的膏状物、腮红和粉末摆在桌面上。",
        "MovieTheater_Governor": "Governor: It's lovely to see economic development in the valley! / 州长：很高兴看到谷里的经济发展成果！",
        "ArchaeologyHouse.4": "A Geological History Of Stardew Valley / 星露谷地质历史",
        "HaleyHouse.8": "It's Emily's computer. It's password-protected so you can't snoop around on it. / 这是艾米丽的计算机。设有密码保护，所以你不能窥探里面的内容。",
        "AnimalShop.19": "Looks like someone was chopping vegetables but never finished. / 好像有人曾在这里切菜，但是没切完。",
        "MovieTheater_Lupini": "Lupini: Amateurs! The set design was completely mundane! / 卢皮尼：真是业余！这布景设计普通至极！",
        "MovieTheater_CraneMan2": "Crane Man: Almost... got it... / 抓娃娃的人：差一点……就抓到了……",
        "JojaMart.72": "Powdered wine / 粉末状酒精",
        "JojaMart.51": "Powdered breakfast -- Just add water. (Eggs & Potatoes) / 粉状早餐——只需加水。（鸡蛋和土豆）",
        "HarveyRoom.9": "'The Lone Ranger Of Pulmonary Hypertension' / “孤独的肺动脉高压巡逻骑兵”",
        "FishShop.5": "Well, it's a bin full of writhing, wriggling worms. It smells something awful. / 嗯，这箱子里装满了扭来扭去的虫子。味道难闻极了。",
        "JojaMart.54": "Brown bread / 黑面包",
        "JojaMart.33": "Floss / 牙线",
        "ScienceHouse.1": "Space poster / 太空海报",
        "JojaMart.57": "Unbearable torturous blaze sauce / 痛苦难耐之火焰酱",
        "MovieTheater_Mother": "Woman: Simon, don't you want something healthy? *sigh*... okay... / 妇女：西蒙，你不想要吃点健康的吗？唉……好吧……",
        "MovieTheater_Welwick2": "Welwick: I foresee great things in your future... If you buy lots of tickets to this movie! / 维尔维克：我预见到你未来会有伟大的成就……如果你买很多张这部电影的票！",
        "JoshHouse.7": "You peek into Alex's drawer. There's clothes, hair gel, and a box of gridball trading cards. / 你偷看了下亚历克斯的抽屉。里面有衣服、发胶以及一个装着格球交易卡的盒子。",
        "Blacksmith.4": "Dear Emily, / 亲爱的艾米丽，^I know you only think of me as a friend.^It's my fault. I'm too shy. I'll never have the courage to tell you the truth.^That's why I'm writing this letter to myself that I'll certainly crumple up and toss in the corner. / 我知道你只是把我当成朋友而已。^这是我的错。我太害羞了。我始终无法鼓起勇气向你说实话。^这就是为什么我要给自己写这封信，而且写完后我一定会把这信给揉成一团然后扔到墙角。",
        "HaleyHouse.4": "It's a mini futan bear! / 这是一个迷你福坦熊！",
        "HaleyHouse.2": "You quickly peek into Haley's private dresser. It's stuffed with clothes.  / 你很快地瞄了一下海莉的私人衣柜。里面塞满了衣服。",
        "JojaMart.85": "Fruit snacks / 水果零食",
        "IslandShrine_Shrine": "When dark clouds cry, begin your quest / 黑云落泪时，征程即开始^To seek the fabled gem-birds four^Each day, one north, south, east, or west^Arrange their gifts upon my door / 传说之中宝石鸟，共有四只待寻找^每日一只方位变，东南西北现^置其馈礼我门前",
        "JojaMart.40": "Yeast / 酵母",
        "Farm_Mining.1": "Grandpa's Shrine / 爷爷的神龛",
        "BathHouse_MensLocker.2": "Trying to shower with your clothes on? / 想要穿着衣服淋浴吗？",
        "JojaMart.74": "Gummies / 软糖",
        "WitchHut.6": "You try not to make eye contact... / 你试着避免眼神交流……",
        "HaleyHouse.14": "It's a globe. Hey, there's Stardew Valley! / 这是一个地球仪。嘿，看到星露谷了！",
        "ScienceHouse.9": "Lots of soda. / 大量苏打。",
        "JojaMart.39": "Pesto / 香蒜沙司",
        "JojaMart.70": "X-treme Chipz / 极限炸土豆条",
        "HarveyRoom.12": "It's full of convenience food. / 它里面装满了便利食品。",
        "HarveyRoom.13": "\"Ground-To-Air Radio Protocol\" / “地对空无线电通讯协议”",
        "Blacksmith.5": "It's a professional-grade furnace. Peering inside, you see molten metal bubbling and churning. / 这是一个专业级的火炉。往里仔细瞧，你会看到被烧熔的金属正在冒泡和翻腾。",
        "JojaMart.30": "Drinkable Frosting / 饮用糖霜",
        "JojaMart.7": "Protein bars / 蛋白棒",
        "SamHouse.6": "There's a bunch of extra strong hair gel in here. / 这里有很多高强度的发胶。",
        "JojaMart.84": "Canned scrambled eggs / 炒鸡蛋罐头",
        "HaleyHouse.16": "Cupcakes, milk, a tightly sealed jar of cornichons, and quinoa salad. / 纸杯蛋糕、牛奶、一罐密封酸黄瓜和奎藜籽色拉。",
        "MovieTheater_Gunther": "Hey, I'd love to chat, but I need to head back to the museum! / 嘿，我很想聊天，但我得回博物馆去了！",
        "JojaMart.36": "Canned shrimp. / 罐装虾。",
        "FishShop.3": "Miniature model of a frigate. / 护卫舰的微缩模型。",
        "AnimalShop.11": "How To Raise Chickens / 如何养鸡",
        "ScienceHouse.12": "Beaker set. / 烧杯集",
        "Trailer.1": "'Teacher's Guidebook: 2nd Grade' / “教师指南书：2 年级”",
        "JojaMart.13": "Canned soup / 罐装羹",
        "JoshHouse.9": "It's Alex's gridball helmet. Looks like he keeps it polished. / 这是亚历克斯的格球头盔。他把它擦得很亮。",
        "MovieTheater_Child": "Simon: Mom! I want candy! *slurp* / 西蒙：妈妈！我要糖果！（咂嘴）",
        "Pirates5": "GRIM PIRATE: From yonder seas, a chilling tale, a nightmare sure to haunt your sleep...#'Twas midnight when I lost me hands... to a savage monster o' the deep...#Yar, 'tis true...#...#...#..............#..............................................#Alright, I'm just kidding. I actually lost them while trying to fish an eggshell out of the blender.#Alas... me famous cake batter days are over... / 阴冷的海盗：在海的那一头，惊悚的故事，噩梦令你无法安眠……#半夜里我失去了双手……是一个凶恶的深渊野兽……#嗯，是真的……#……#……#………………#………………………………………………#好吧，我开玩笑呢。我是想从一个搅拌机里面钓出一个蛋壳才丢了我的手的。#哎呀……蛋糕的好日子一去不复返了……",
        "AnimalShop.4": "The little family is gathered around the dinner table. Wait... except Grandpa. He's wedged under the bed for some reason. / 小家庭围坐在餐桌边。等等……除了爷爷。出于某种原因，他挤到了床底下。",
        "JojaMart.99": "Canned meals / 罐头食物",
        "JojaMart.46": "Take-Me-To-The-Emergency-Room sauce / “带我去急诊室”酱",
        "WitchHut.1": "Whoever lives here must really like a clean floor! / 住在这的人一定很喜欢干净的地板！",
        "JoshHouse.14": "It's empty. / 它是空的。",
        "HarveyRoom.14": "It's a pretty standard TV set. It's set to the history station. / 这是一台相当标准的电视机。它被设置到了历史频道。",
        "HaleyHouse.3": "You quickly peek into Haley's private dresser. It's stuffed with clothes.  / 你很快地瞄了一下海莉的私人衣柜。里面塞满了衣服。",
        "Pirates2": "RED: Mamma mia! Calm down, brother. Youch! / 小红：妈妈咪呀！冷静点，老哥。哎呦喂！",
        "Hospital.6": "This clinic is licensed for medical practice by the Ferngill Republic Health Authority. / 该诊所经芬吉尔共和国卫生当局批准，可以对病人进行诊疗。",
        "SeedShop.8": "'Why JojaCo Must Be Stopped' / “为什么必须制止 Joja 公司”",
        "Hospital.5": "'Don't spread disease... Cover your sneeze!' / “不要传播病菌……挡一下你的喷嚏！”",
        "JojaMart.58": "Sugar cones / 宝塔糖",
        "JojaMart.31": "Sprouted wheat bread / 全麦面包",
        "JojaMart.20": "Grade D Cooking Oil / D 级食用油",
        "JojaMart.3": "Sugar-free marshmallows / 无糖棉花糖",
        "LeahHouse.2": "It's a stack of Leah's paintings. It's mostly landscapes and studies of nature. / 这是一堆莉亚的画。主要是风景画和对自然的观察。",
        "MovieTheater_Child2": "Simon: Mom! I want chocolate popcorn! *slurp* / 西蒙：妈妈！我要巧克力爆米花！（咂嘴）",
        "AnimalShop.21": "Mostly empty pizza cartons. / 多半是空的披萨盒。",
        "Town-Fair.8": " Archaeology Office - Open 8:00 AM to 6:00 PM / 考古学办公室 - 开放时间上午 8:00 到下午 6:00",
        "SeedShop.5": "'Parenting 101:Surviving The Teenage Years' / “父母课程 101：如何应对成长为青少年的孩子”",
        "BathHouse_MensLocker.4": "Alex's Locker... There's a bunch of pictures of bodybuilders taped inside the door. / 亚历克斯的储物柜……门内贴有一堆健美运动员的图片。",
        "SamHouse.3": "Jodi- / 约迪：^Since I'll be coming home soon I want to tell you a few things.^I might not be the same man you remember. I've seen some things out here that have really shaken me up. I've been having a real hard time relaxing.^I don't want to scare you or make you upset. I just don't want you to be shocked when I get back.^Remember, no matter how I act, you and the kids mean everything to me.^I'll see you soon.^-Kent / 因为我很快就会回家，因此我想先告诉你几件事。^我可能和你记忆中的我有很大的不同。我在外面看到了某些事情，让我感到十分震撼，最近我的精神一直紧绷着，无法放松。^我不想吓到你或者让你感到不安，我只是不想让你见到我时感到震惊。^记住，无论我在你面前表现的有多奇怪，你和孩子始终是我的一切。^我们很快会见面。^——肯特",
        "FishShop.6": "Chum bucket. / 海之霸餐厅。",
        "Blacksmith.6": "It's a professional-grade furnace. Peering inside, you see molten metal bubbling and churning. / 这是一个专业级的火炉。往里仔细瞧，你会看到被烧熔的金属正在冒泡和翻腾。",
        "HarveyRoom.11": "It looks well used. / 这个看起来很好用。",
        "JojaMart.49": "Sugar cane chips / 甘蔗薯条",
        "LeahHouse.3": "'Living Off The Land: A Practical Guide' / “离地而居：使用手册”",
        "SamHouse.9": "Sam's electric guitar. It has a pair of active pickups and a whammy bar. / 萨姆的电吉他。它有一对主动拾音器和一个摇把。",
        "SamHouse.7": "There's a bunch of skateboarding magazines. / 有很多滑板杂志。",
        "Pirates6": "He's in a stupor... / 他昏过去了……",
        "JoshHouse.11": "It's a well-stocked refrigerator. / 这是一个装满食物的冰箱。",
        "MovieTheater_Governor2": "Governor: I really must bring the missus out for soup and a movie! / 州长：我一定要带太太出来到这吃个饭，看场电影！",
        "Pirates7_1": "DART MAN: How about we make things more interesting. Hit exactly 301 points within 15 darts and I'll be impressed, matey! / 飞镖伙计：再来点有意思的如何？伙计，15 镖之内投出 301 分整，那你了不起！",
        "Hospital.7": "Hey, this plant's fake! / 嘿，这个植物是假的！",
        "Pirates7_3": "DART MAN: Ahoy! If it isn't me matey... ol' steady-hands! How about a game o' darts for old times' sake? / 飞镖伙计：啊嘿！又是你啊……老手！再来一局飞镖如何？",
        "JojaMart.90": "Canola oil / 菜籽油",
        "LeahHouse.4": "'How To Deal With Overbearing People' / “如何应对人口的过度繁殖”",
        "HarveyRoom.2": "There's a beautiful view of the sky above Stardew Valley. / 星露谷上方的天空十分美丽。",
        "JojaMart.103": "Extra Pure Olive-flavored oil / 特纯橄榄油",
        "LeahHouse.1": "It's a work in progress. / 这个作品还未完工。",
        "JojaMart.37": "Cinnamon sugar chips / 肉桂糖薯条",
        "ElliottHouse.1": "It's a painting by Leah. / 这是利亚的一幅画。",
        "JojaMart.108": "Corn flour. / 玉米粉。",
        "JojaMart.56": "Toothpaste / 牙膏",
        "ElliottHouse.2": "Elliott's work desk. It's covered in notes and crumpled papers. / 艾利欧特的办公桌。上面堆满了笔记和揉皱的纸团。",
        "JojaMart.59": "Budget wine / 廉价酒",
        "MovieTheater_CranePlay": "Play the Crane Game? (Costs {0}g) / 玩抓娃娃机？（花费 {0} 金）",
        "Pirates7_Win_Perfect": "DART MAN: Well, shiver me timbers! That's a perfect game! / 飞镖伙计：哇塞，太牛啦！这一局完美！",
        "JojaMart.1": "Hoisin sauce / 海鲜酱",
        "MovieTheater_RedCapGuy2": "Man: I sat in the front row... big mistake. / 男性：坐在前排位置……这真是重大失误。",
        "MovieTheater_Gunther2": "Hey, @. I just saw the movie, myself... not bad! / 嘿，@。我刚刚看了电影，独自一人……感觉还不错！",
        "ArchaeologyHouse.3": "Journeys Across The Gem Sea / 跨越宝石海的旅行",
        "ArchaeologyHouse.6": "Star Atlas / 星图",
        "JojaMart.71": "X-treme chips with Inferno Sauce / 极限炸土豆条配地狱酱",
        "MovieTheater_CraneOccupied": "The crane game is in use by someone else. / 其他人还在玩抓娃娃机。",
        "MovieTheater_Morris": "As you can see, the theater is a major success!$h#$b#Whaa...? A return on your investment? Well, it's difficult, you know... might take a while, you understand... *mumble*$2 / 如你所见，电影获得了巨大成功！$h#$b#啥……？你的投资回报？嗯，这有点困难，那个……可能需要花上一段时间，请理解……（咕哝）$2",
        "LeahHouse.5": "It's a wooden sculpture Leah's working on. It has a wonderful cedar smell. / 这是莉亚正在做的木质雕塑。它有一股芬香的雪松味。",
        "SeedShop.12": "This cupboard is full of exercise equipment. / 这个柜子中全是健身设备。",
        "MovieTheater_Lupini2": "Lupini: Amateurs! My nephew's 2nd birthday party home video had better cinematography! / 卢皮尼：真是业余！我侄子的两岁生日派对的纪念视频摄影水平都比这高！",
        "Town-Christmas.2": "It's old and faded... / 很古老，而且都褪色了……",
        "JojaMart.26": "JojaDiet -- Low fat beans! In a sweet sugar-sauce / Joja 减肥产品——低脂豆子！蘸香甜糖酱",
        "ArchaeologyHouse.7": "It's ragged but still cute. / 它衣衫褴褛，但仍然可爱。",
        "JojaMart.78": "Sourdough bread / 酵母面包",
        "Town.4": "\"Our Beloved Mona\" / “我们亲爱的莫娜”",
        "JojaMart.32": "Partially-Hydrogenated Corn Oil / 部分氢化玉米油",
        "SamHouse.2": "Eggs, bread, carrots, and milk. / 鸡蛋、面包、胡萝卜和牛奶。",
        "MovieTheater_Marlon": "Gil slept through the whole movie... typical. / 吉尔整部电影都在睡觉……不出所料。",
        "SamHouse.12": "Vincent's toys are strewn about the room. / 文森特的玩具散落在房间各处。",
        "Forest.1": "` Farm / ` 农场^> Pelican Town / > 鹈鹕镇",
        "HarveyRoom.5": "It's a complicated radio broadcasting set. / 这是一个复杂的无线电台广播组。",
        "Pirates7_WinPrize": "Here's a little something for ya. / 给你一点好玩意儿。",
        "HaleyHouse.15": "The oven smells sweet like fresh cupcakes. / 炉子闻起来很甜就像刚出炉的纸杯蛋糕。",
        "Blacksmith.7": "Clint's quality anvil. It's made from an iridium alloy. / 克林特的优质铁砧，由铱合金制成。",
        "Mountain.1": "` Railroad  / ` 铁路 ",
        "JojaMart.38": "White fungus soda / 银耳苏打水",
        "AnimalShop.2": "Ah... an extra large futan bear! It's so plush it can hardly stop from toppling over. / 啊……一个超大福坦熊！它如此毛绒绒的，总是让人忍不住想要推倒。",
        "HaleyHouse.5": "It's an empty diary. / 这是一本空的日记簿。",
        "MovieTheater_CraneMan": "Crane Man: Can't talk... I'm in the zone. / 抓娃娃的人：没法说话……我在专心。",
        "AnimalShop.1": "Ah... an extra large futan bear! It's so plush it can hardly stop from toppling over. / 啊……一个超大福坦熊！它如此毛绒绒的，总是让人忍不住想要推倒。",
        "JojaMart.15": "JojaCo Multipurpose sauce / Joja 公司 万能酱",
        "Town.5": " Archaeology Office - Open 8:00 AM to 6:00 PM / 考古学办公室 - 开放时间上午 8:00 到下午 6:00",
        "SamHouse.4": "It's set to the news station. / 它被设置到了新闻台。",
        "Club.1": "Welwick: It's not my lucky day. Ugh... I drank too much. / 维尔维克：今天我可真倒霉。嗝……我喝太多了。",
        "FishShop.1": "It leads up to a little sleeping cubby. It's off limits. / 它通向一个小型睡眠用房间。那里禁止进入。",
        "FishShop.7": "Looks like frog eggs. / 看起来像蛙卵。",
        "ScienceHouse.5": "'Advanced Neural Networks' / \"先进的神经网络\"",
        "Town-Christmas.3": "\"Our Beloved Mona\" / “我们亲爱的莫娜”",
        "ElliottHouse.6": "It looks like Elliott is trying to grow a bonsai tree. It looks cool so far! / 看起来，艾利欧特打算种植一个盆栽。它看起来酷呆了！",
        "Town-EggFestival.3": "\"Our Beloved Mona\" / “我们亲爱的莫娜”",
        "JojaMart.101": "Blue-Green sugar orbs / 蓝绿色糖球",
        "JojaMart.27": "Marinara sauce / 番茄蒜味酱",
        "JojaMart.64": "Explosion Juice / 爆炸果汁",
        "JojaMart.28": "100% pure honey-flavored 'sauce' / 100% 纯蜂蜜口味“酱”",
        "JojaMart.42": "Cocoa Zeppelins / 可可飞艇",
        "JojaMart.6": "Salt / 盐",
        "JoshHouse.2": "The radio is set to the oldies station. / 无线电被调到老歌电台。",
        "ArchaeologyHouse.5": "Calico Desert Flora & Fauna / 印花布沙漠植物区系和动物区系",
        "HaleyHouse.11": "It's Haley's camera. / 这是海莉的相机。",
        "Town-Christmas.1": "Clinic - Hours 9:00 AM - 3:00 PM / 门诊时间——上午 9:00——下午 3:00 ",
        "Town-EggFestival.1": "Clinic - Hours 9:00 AM - 3:00 PM / 门诊时间——上午 9:00 ——下午 3:00",
        "JojaMart.92": "Fire Sauce / 火酱",
        "AnimalShop.14": "A little paint set. / 一个小颜料盒。",
        "JojaMart.25": "Barbecue smokehouse chips with mesquite flavoring / 牧豆味烧烤熏制薯条",
        "SamHouse.11": "It's Sam's computer. He's got an extensive library of computer games. / 这是萨姆的电脑。他电脑中有海量电脑游戏。",
        "Town-EggFestival.4": " Archaeology Office - Open 8:00 AM to 6:00 PM /  考古学办公室 - 开放时间上午 8:00 到下午 6:00",
        "Hospital.2": "It's a sample jar. Better not put your fingers in there. / 这是一个样品罐。最好不要把你的手放到里面去。",
        "SeedShop.9": "To Mr. Pierre: / 皮埃尔先生:^It pains me to be the bearer of bad news, but I feel obligated to inform you of a recent development most threatening to your livelihood.^Joja Co. has decided to expand into Pelican Town.^It's too late for protest. Joja Builders have already broken ground for the new JojaMart.^^This must be devastating news for you. So many years in business...a local standby... and now, obscured by the shadow of a powerful, efficient, economically viable corporation. What a shame!^^As manager of the new JojaMart, I feel, to some degree, personally responsible for your predicament. As such, I'd like to offer you a position as Assistant Grocer. Wages start at 5g an hour. I look forward to seeing your resume!^^-Mr. Morris, Manager^Pelican Town JojaMart / 我真不想告诉您这个坏消息，但最近有些事会威胁到你的生计，因此我有义务告诉你。^Joja 公司已经决定扩展到鹈鹕镇。^现在抗议已经太迟了。Joja 建筑商已经为新的 Joja 超市破土动工了。^^这对你来说肯定是最糟糕的消息，你在这行干了这么多年……一直为当地人供给粮食……而现在，一个强大高效且资金雄厚的公司却把你的生意给抢走了。多可惜！^^作为 Joja 超市的新经理，我感觉自己需要对你目前所处的困境承担一定的责任。因此，我想让你担任助理杂货商。工资从每小时 5 金开始。我期待看到你的简历！^^——莫里斯先生，经理^鹈鹕镇 Joja 超市",
        "AnimalShop.15": "There's an antique clock and a little golden trinket box. / 有一个古董钟和一个金色饰品盒。",
        "Trailer.2": "'Marcie And The Underground Castle' / “马西和地下城堡”",
        "ArchaeologyHouse.9": "Let's visit the farm. The chickens go bock bock. The pigs go snort snort. The goats go mah mah.#The ducks go ack ack. The rabbits go sniff sniff. The cows go ooh ooh. / 我们参观农场吧。鸡儿喔喔喔，猪儿哼哼哼，山羊咩咩咩。#鸭子嘎嘎嘎。兔子咕咕咕。牛儿哞哞哞。",
        "Hospital.1": "The sign of the vessel. It's here to comfort those who believe in Yoba. / 舰形符号。这是用来抚慰那些信仰由巴的人的。",
        "HaleyHouse.7": "It's a bolt of blue cloth. There's pieces cut out of it, and little embroidered patterns along the fringe. / 这是一匹蓝布。上面有一些布头被剪去了，边缘处绣有小型花纹。",
        "SeedShop.6": "It's loaded with fresh veggies. / 上面装满了新鲜蔬菜。",
        "Town-Fair.5": "Tourist: It was a long bus ride here, but totally worth it! This valley is so beautiful. Simon loves it... don't you, Simon? / 游客：我坐了很长时间的公共汽车才抵达这里，但这趟旅程是完全值得的！这个山谷真美丽啊，西蒙很喜欢它……对吧，西蒙？",
        "ScienceHouse.3": "'Maximizing Your Second Marriage' and 'Practical Tips For First-Time Step-Dads' / “最大化你的二次婚姻”和“初次继父实用小贴士”",
        "Blacksmith.9": "There's a stack of metalworking blueprints. / 有一堆金属加工图。",
        "Blacksmith.8": "Clint's quality anvil. It's made from an iridium alloy. / 克林特的优质铁砧，由铱合金制成。",
        "MovieTheater_Marcello2": "Marcello: What a spread! I think I'll go for the 12-grain spicy mustard. Hehe! / 马塞罗：这电影真难看！我觉得我得来点 12 粒辣芥末。呵呵！",
        "Club.2": "Man: Hey, can't you see I'm busy? I'm on a roll here. / 男：哎，你没看我正忙着吗？简直忙得脚不沾地。",
        "JojaMart.29": "White fungus soda / 银耳苏打水",
        "SamHouse.8": "'UFO Mysteries' / “不明飞行物之谜”",
        "JoshHouse.5": "'Mega Muscles' magazine / “超级肌肉”杂志",
        "JoshHouse.13": "'The Dark Blue Life: A Coal-miner's Memoir' / “深蓝色生活：一个煤炭工人的回忆录”",
        "MovieTheater_ShortsMan2": "Corner Guy: Psst... I just saw the movie, and... Relax! I'm not going to spoil it for you. / 街角小子：嘘……我刚看了电影，而且……放轻松！我不会给你剧透的。",
        "Pirates4": "BLACKGULL: Yar, matey. Ye must have a keen eye to've spotted our secret cove. Yo ho! / 黑海鸥：嘿，伙计。能找到我们的秘密海湾，你眼睛很尖嘛。呦吼！",
        "HaleyHouse.9": "'Found Fashions: Photos From The Streets Of Zuzu City' / “发现时尚：来自祖祖城市街道的照片”",
        "AnimalShop.9": "Jack-in-the-box is sprawled out, his arms bent at grotesque angles. His hollow eyes peer coldly into the distance. / 玩偶盒掉在地上，玩偶的胳膊以奇怪的角度弯曲着。他空洞的双眼冷冷地看向远处。",
        "PirateBartender_PirateClothes": "BARTENDER: Oi! I never seen the likes o' you, before. But if ye got the pirate look, then 'ave one on me! Har Har! / 酒保：喂！我以前没看到过像你这样的人。不过如果你看起来像海盗，那我可以请你一杯！哈哈！",
        "PirateBartender_PirateClothes_NoMore": "BARTENDER: Back fer more, eh? Har Har! You've had enough, matey... / 酒保：啊，还想要？哈哈！你喝得够多了，伙计……",
        "Pirates3": "WELL-DRESSED PIRATE: *ahem*... Yar.#...#...Not convincing, huh?#*sigh*...#To tell you the truth, I don't really want to be a pirate. I'd rather grow palms.#Unfortunately, there's no money in the palm business... / 穿着考究的海盗：咳咳……嗯。#……#……是不是没什么说服力？#唉……#说实话，我是真的不想当海盗。我宁愿去种棕榈树。#可惜的是，做棕榈树生意并不挣钱……",
        "SamHouse.10": "--Report Card-- / ——成绩单——^Name: Vincent^^Reading: C^Spelling: D^Math: C^Social Studies: B-^Art: B-^Sports:A^^Note:Vince is a good boy, but he could make do with a little more studying!^  -Penny / 名字：文森特^^朗读：C^拼写：D^数学：C^社会研究：B-^美术：B-^体育：A^^备注：文森特是个好孩子，但是他还需要更加努力！^  ——潘妮",
        "JoshHouse.1": "Momma- / 妈妈：^If you're reading this, it means I've passed on. I'm so sorry you had to go through this. Know that I love you both.^Don't be too upset, I'm with Yoba now. ^My final request: take care of Alex. He needs a family, something stable. He's a good kid.^ Love, ^Clara / 如果你看到了这封信，那就说明我已经去世了。我很抱歉你不得不承受这一切。我爱你们两个人。^别太难过，我现在已经去了由巴那里。^我最后的要求：照顾好亚历克斯。他需要一个家，需要能好好照顾他的家人。他是一个好孩子。^ 我爱你们，^克莱拉",
        "BusStop.1": "` Bus Stop / ` 公交车站^> Pelican Town / > 鹈鹕镇",
        "JojaMart.82": "Gummies / 软糖",
        "JojaMart.52": "Jitter Juice / 颤动果汁",
        "JojaMart.44": "Synthetic Butter -- It's cheap! / 人造黄油——很便宜！",
        "ArchaeologyHouse.1": "A History of The Gotoro Empire / 戈特洛国历史",
        "JojaMart.66": "Powdered butter / 黄油粉",
        "JojaMart.100": "JojaCola AMPED / Joja 公司 AMPED",
        "FishShop.4": "There's little pink shrimps moving around in there. / 里面只粉红色的小虾米在爬来爬去。",
        "JojaMart.61": "Vegan sausage / 素肠",
        "JojaMart.87": "Hyper Juice / 超级果汁",
        "JojaMart.69": "Sugar stars / 糖果星星",
        "HarveyRoom.6": "It's a complicated radio broadcasting set. / 这是一个复杂的无线电台广播组。",
        "Farm_Combat.1": "Grandpa's Shrine / 爷爷的神龛",
        "JojaMart.65": "Rye bread / 裸麦面包",
        "Blacksmith.3": "You rifle through Clint's personal effects. There's a stack of blacksmith aprons, some magazines, an old sword, and a nice picture of his mother. / 你翻找着克林特的私人用品。有一堆铁匠围裙、几本杂志、一把旧剑和他母亲的漂亮照片。",
        "AnimalShop.7": "You dig around in Marnie's private drawer. There's nothing of interest. / 你在玛妮的私人抽屉里乱翻。但没发现什么特别的东西。",
        "JojaMart.93": "Fruit snacks / 水果零食",
        "ScienceHouse.11": "One of Robin's axes. / 罗宾的其中一把斧头",
        "Pirates7_Lose": "DART MAN: Yar... Better luck next time... / 飞镖伙计：哎哟……下次好运……",
        "WitchHut.5": "Curse The Countryside!... A Spellbook For The Rural Witch / 诅咒这乡村！……一本农村巫婆的魔法书",
        "Saloon.1": "There's a half-empty mug of beer. / 那有半马克杯啤酒。",
        "JojaMart.75": "Canned scrambled eggs / 炒鸡蛋罐头",
        "JojaMart.81": "Inferno Sauce / 地狱酱",
        "JojaMart.47": "Yeast / 酵母",
        "Town-Halloween.2": "It's old and faded... / 很古老，而且都褪色了……",
        "JojaMart.104": "Laundry Detergent / 洗衣液",
        "HarveyRoom.8": "'Do-It-Yourself! Knee Surgery' / “自己动手做！膝盖手术”",
        "Pirates1": "GREEN: You were always Momma's favorite! WaaaAaAa / 小绿：你总是妈妈最爱的那个！哇啊啊啊",
        "AnimalShop.3": "Junimo Coloring Book -- Deluxe Edition / 祝尼魔彩色书——豪华装",
        "HarveyRoom.3": "It's Harvey's model airplane collection. / 这是哈维的飞机模型收藏。",
        "Town-Fair.3": "Clinic - Hours 9:00 AM - 3:00 PM / 门诊时间——上午 9:00——下午 3:00",
        "HaleyHouse.12": "'Flailing With Purpose: A Modern Approach To The Art Of Dance' / “有计划性的起舞：掌握舞蹈艺术的现代化途径”",
        "Pirates7_2": "DART MAN: Ah, good to see ya again, matey! Let's see if you can score 301 points within... 10 darts! / 飞镖伙计：又见面了，伙计！这次还是投 301 分……10 镖之内！",
        "ScienceHouse.8": "Star charts for every season. / 每一个季节都可使用的星图。",
        "JojaMart.11": "Hair Gel -- Electric Blue / 发胶——铁蓝色",
        "JojaMart.94": "JojaMeal... It's like corn meal but more versatile. It can be used for baking, thickening and sweetening. Mix it with water to make our signature gravy. / Joja 餐……它很像玉米粉，但用法更多。它可用于烘烤、增稠、增甜。把它与水混合可以做成我们的特色肉汁。",
        "ScienceHouse.4": "There's a bunch of carpentry magazines. / 这里有很多木工方面的杂志。",
        "JojaMart.73": "Coconut meat / 椰肉",
        "Town-Fair.1": "Tourist: Man... I can't take another bite of this barbecue sandwich... so stuffed. / 游客:伙计……我不能再吃烤肉三明治了……我撑的太难受了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Strings/Tools",
