      "Entries": {
        "Axe_Iridium_Name": "Iridium Axe / 铱斧头",
        "Axe_Steel_Name": "Steel Axe / 钢斧头",
        "Pan_Iridium_Name": "Iridium Pan / 铱淘盘",
        "TrashCan_Iridium_Name": "Iridium Trash Can / 铱垃圾桶",
        "Pan_Steel_Description": "Use to gather ore from streams. Has bigger and better yields than a copper pan. It also has a small chance to immediately cause another panning spot to appear. / 可以收集河流中的矿石，产出的矿石比铜淘盘更多、品质更好。有小概率立即引出另一个淘金地点。",
