        "Pan_Iridium_Description": "Use to gather ore from streams. Has the best yields of any pan. It also has a chance to immediately cause another panning spot to appear. / 可以收集河流中的矿石，产出的矿石最多、品质最好。有一定概率立即引出另一个淘金地点。",
        "Pickaxe_Steel_Name": "Steel Pickaxe / 钢十字镐",
        "FishingRod_Bamboo_Name": "Bamboo Pole / 竹鱼竿",
        "Hoe_Name": "Hoe / 锄头",
        "WateringCan_Name": "Watering Can / 喷壶",
        "FishingRod_AdvancedIridium_Name": "Advanced Iridium Rod / 高级铱金鱼竿",
        "Hoe_Description": "Used to dig and till soil. / 用于犁地和耕地。",
        "Axe_Copper_Name": "Copper Axe / 铜斧头",
        "Pan_Steel_Name": "Steel Pan / 钢淘盘",
        "Pan_Copper_Name": "Copper Pan / 铜淘盘",
        "WateringCan_Description": "Used to water crops. It can be refilled at any water source. / 用于灌溉作物。可以在任意水源重新装满。",
        "Hoe_Gold_Name": "Gold Hoe / 金锄头",
        "Axe_Gold_Name": "Gold Axe / 金斧头",
        "TrashCan_Description": "When trashing an item, you reclaim {0}% of the value. / 丢弃物品时，你能回收物品价值的 {0}%。",
        "Hoe_Iridium_Name": "Iridium Hoe / 铱锄头",
        "FishingRod_Fiberglass_Name": "Fiberglass Rod / 玻璃纤维棒",
        "Pickaxe_Gold_Name": "Gold Pickaxe / 金十字镐",
        "WateringCan_Iridium_Name": "Iridium Watering Can / 铱喷壶",
        "Pickaxe_Name": "Pickaxe / 十字镐",
        "WateringCan_Steel_Name": "Steel Watering Can / 钢喷壶",
        "FishingRod_AdvancedIridium_Description": "Use in the water to catch fish. Up to two bobbers can be attached at once. / 可以在水中钓鱼。最多同时安装两个浮漂。",
        "MilkPail_Description": "Gather milk from your animals. / 给牲畜挤奶。",
        "Pickaxe_Iridium_Name": "Iridium Pickaxe / 铱十字镐",
        "FishingRod_Description": "Use in the water to catch fish. / 用于在水中捕鱼。",
        "Shears_Description": "Use this to collect wool from sheep. / 用这个来从羊身上剪毛。",
        "Pickaxe_Description": "Used to break stones. / 用来敲碎石头。",
        "Pan_Description": "Use to gather ore from streams. / 用来从溪流中收集矿石。",
        "WateringCan_Copper_Name": "Copper Watering Can / 铜喷壶",
        "Lantern_Description": "Lights up dark places. / 点亮暗处。",
        "Pickaxe_Copper_Name": "Copper Pickaxe / 铜十字镐",
        "MilkPail_Name": "Milk Pail / 挤奶桶",
        "Axe_Name": "Axe / 斧头",
        "ReturnScepter_Description": "The golden handle quivers with raw potential. Hold this scepter to the sky and return home at will. / 金光闪闪的手柄中蕴含着巨大的原始魔力。手持这个魔杖指向天空就可以随时回家。",
        "WateringCan_Gold_Name": "Gold Watering Can / 金喷壶",
