        "Character_CoopHelpString": "Starting Cabins: Start with 1-{0} cabins already in place, allowing your friends to join immediately. Alternatively, you can select \"None\" and build the cabins yourself (via Robin). / 初始联机小屋：开始时已有 1 至 {0} 间联机小屋就位，可让你的朋友立即加入。或者，你可以选择“无”，并（通过罗宾）自己建造联机小屋。^^Cabin Layout: If you decide to start your farm with pre-existing cabins, you can choose between two layout styles: \"Nearby\" places all cabins near the main farmhouse, encouraging a communal farming style. \"Separate\" places the cabins far apart, allowing more room for independence.^^Profit Margin: Adjusts the profit margin (money you earn) on goods you sell. 'Normal' is the original Stardew Valley experience. More experienced and/or larger groups may wish to decrease the margin. / ^联机小屋布局：如果你决定用原本存在的联机小屋开始你的农场，则可在两种布局风格之间做选择：“附近”将所有联机小屋都放在主农舍附近，鼓励社区型耕种风格。“独立”将尽可能拉开联机小屋之间的距离，提供更多的独立空间。^^利润率：调节你所出售商品的利润率（你赚的钱）。“普通”是原汁原味的星露谷体验。经验较丰富和/或规模较大的团队员可能会压低利润。",
        "LevelUp_ProfessionDescription_Trapper": "Resources required to craft crab pots reduced. / 制造蟹笼所需的材料用量减少。",
