        "InfinityGavel_Name": "Infinity Gavel / 无限之锤",
        "HolyBlade_Name": "Holy Blade / 圣剑",
        "WoodClub_Description": "A solid piece of wood, crudely chiseled into a club shape. / 沉重的木，粗糙地打造成棍子的型状。",
        "BoneSword_Name": "Bone Sword / 骨剑",
        "SteelSmallsword_Description": "A standard metal blade. / 一把标准的金属刀。",
        "LeahsWhittler_Name": "Leah's Whittler / 莉亚的削木刀",
        "TemperedBroadsword_Name": "Tempered Broadsword / 淬火阔剑",
        "BurglarsShank_Name": "Burglar's Shank / 飞贼之胫",
        "SebsLostMace_Name": "Seb's Lost Mace / 塞巴斯蒂安的遗失之锤",
        "SteelSmallsword_Name": "Steel Smallsword / 钢制轻剑",
        "HaleysIron_Description": "It's searing hot and smells like Haley's hair. / 非常烫手，散发着跟海莉的头发一样的味道。",
        "MarusWrench_Description": "A big, metal wrench. It smells like Maru. / 巨大的金属扳手。闻起来很有玛鲁的味道。",
        "BurglarsShank_Description": "A weapon of choice for the swift and silent. / 身手敏捷、行动隐秘的人首选之武器。",
        "ElfBlade_Description": "Only the nimble hands of an elf could craft this. / 唯有精灵的巧手才能打造出这件物品。",
        "BrokenTrident_Name": "Broken Trident / 残破的三叉戟",
        "IridiumNeedle_Description": "The point is unbelievably sharp, even down to the atomic level. / 其尖锐超出想象，甚至微观到原子层面也是无比尖锐。",
        "AlexsBat_Name": "Alex's Bat / 亚历克斯的棒球棍",
        "GalaxyDagger_Name": "Galaxy Dagger / 银河匕首",
        "SamsOldGuitar_Description": "It's seen better days. / 陈旧落魄。",
        "RustySword_Description": "A rusty, dull old sword. / 一把又锈又旧的钝剑。",
        "Slingshot_Description": "Requires stones for ammo. / 需要石子当弹药。",
        "Scythe_Description": "It can cut grass into hay, if you've built a silo. / 如果你建了一个筒仓，它可以割草以及收获干草。",
        "IronEdge_Name": "Iron Edge / 铁刃",
        "Claymore_Description": "It's really heavy. / 非常沉重。",
        "SebsLostMace_Description": "One of Sebastian's medieval replicas. / 塞巴斯蒂安的中世纪仿制品之一。",
        "SteelFalchion_Description": "Light and powerful. / 轻便，威力强大。",
        "GalaxySlingshot_Description": "It looks really powerful. / 看上去很强大。",
        "LeadRod_Description": "It's incredibly heavy. / 异常的沉。",
        "MasterSlingshot_Name": "Master Slingshot / 高级弹弓",
        "Kudgel_Name": "Kudgel / 长柄锤",
        "AbbysPlanchette_Description": "It's made from fine marblewood. / 用大理石木打造而成。",
        "CarvingKnife_Name": "Carving Knife / 刻刀",
        "ObsidianEdge_Name": "Obsidian Edge / 黑曜石之刃",
        "GalaxySword_Name": "Galaxy Sword / 银河剑",
        "Meowmere_Name": "Meowmere / 彩虹猫之刃",
        "IridiumScythe_Name": "Iridium Scythe / 铱镰刀",
        "YetiTooth_Name": "Yeti Tooth / 雪怪之牙",
        "DragontoothCutlass_Name": "Dragontooth Cutlass / 龙牙弯刀",
        "WoodenBlade_Description": "Not bad for a piece of carved wood. / 对于一块木雕来说不错了。",
        "WindSpire_Description": "A swift little blade. / 轻便的小刀。",
        "InfinityBlade_Description": "The true form of the Galaxy Sword. / 银河剑的真实形态。",
        "HaleysIron_Name": "Haley's Iron / 海莉的烫发棒",
        "IronEdge_Description": "A heavy broadsword. / 很重的阔剑。",
        "RustySword_Name": "Rusty Sword / 生锈的剑",
        "Rapier_Description": "An elegant blade. / 一把优雅的剑。",
        "Cutlass_Name": "Cutlass / 弯刀",
        "TemperedBroadsword_Description": "It looks like it could withstand anything. / 看上去能够抵挡任何东西。",
        "WoodMallet_Description": "The solid head packs a punch. Relatively light for a club. / 坚固的头部威力强大。对于一把棍棒来说，重量有点轻。",
        "LeadRod_Name": "Lead Rod / 铅棒",
        "WoodClub_Name": "Wood Club / 木棒",
        "PennysFryer_Name": "Penny's Fryer / 潘妮的煎锅",
        "WickedKris_Name": "Wicked Kris / 蛇形邪剑",
        "IridiumScythe_Description": "Can be used to harvest any crops. It's also excellent at gathering hay. / 可以收割所有作物，收集干草效果极佳。",
        "LavaKatana_Name": "Lava Katana / 熔岩武士刀",
        "DragontoothClub_Description": "This club was crafted from a magical tooth. / 这根棍子是用一颗充满魔力的牙齿锻造而成的。",
        "TemplarsBlade_Description": "It once belonged to an honorable knight. / 曾属于一位高尚的圣殿骑士。",
        "NeptunesGlaive_Name": "Neptune's Glaive / 海王星大剑",
        "YetiTooth_Description": "It's icy cold to the touch. / 寒冷冻人。",
        "NeptunesGlaive_Description": "An heirloom from beyond the Gem Sea. / 来自宝石海的传家宝。",
        "WickedKris_Description": "The blade is made of an iridium alloy. / 使用铱合金打造的刀刃。",
        "DwarfDagger_Description": "It's ancient, but the blade never dulls. / 它很古老，但刃锋未曾变钝。",
        "BrokenTrident_Description": "It came from the sea, but it's still sharp. / 来自海洋，依然尖锐。",
        "IridiumNeedle_Name": "Iridium Needle / 铱针",
        "GalaxyHammer_Name": "Galaxy Hammer / 银河之锤",
        "InsectHead_Name": "Insect Head / 昆虫头部",
        "ForestSword_Description": "Made powerful by forest magic. / 由森林魔法打造的强力之剑。",
        "SteelFalchion_Name": "Steel Falchion / 钢刀",
        "GoldenScythe_Description": "It's more powerful than a normal scythe. / 它比传统的镰刀更强大。",
        "ElliottsPencil_Name": "Elliott's Pencil / 艾利欧特的铅笔",
        "InfinityGavel_Description": "The true form of the Galaxy Hammer. / 银河之锤的真实形态。",
        "SilverSaber_Name": "Silver Saber / 镀银军刀",
        "InsectHead_Description": "Not very pleasant to wield. / 挥起来很不舒服。",
        "Femur_Name": "Femur / 股骨",
        "Meowmere_Description": "An unusual weapon from a far away land... / 来自异界的罕见武器……",
        "IronDirk_Description": "A common dagger. / 一把普通的匕首。",
        "DwarfHammer_Description": "It emits a very faint whirring sound. / 它会发出微弱的嗡嗡声。",
        "BoneSword_Description": "A very light piece of sharpened bone. / 磨尖的骨头打造的轻剑。",
        "Femur_Description": "An old, heavy bone caked in centuries of grime. / 一根古老沉重的骨头，覆盖着数个世纪的尘垢。",
        "GoldenScythe_Name": "Golden Scythe / 金色的镰刀",
        "Kudgel_Description": "A brute's companion. / 野蛮人的最佳伙伴。",
        "PennysFryer_Description": "Penny's favorite frying pan. There's some rubbery gunk stuck to the inside. / 潘妮最爱的煎锅。里面凝固着一些胶状物。",
        "ShadowDagger_Description": "When you hold the blade to your ear you can hear 1,000 souls shrieking. / 把刀放到耳旁，能听见千百条灵魂的哀嚎。",
        "Claymore_Name": "Claymore / 双刃大剑",
        "OssifiedBlade_Name": "Ossified Blade / 骨化剑",
        "GalaxyHammer_Description": "It's made from an ultra-light material you've never seen before. / 用一种你闻所未闻的超轻材料打造而成。",
        "IronDirk_Name": "Iron Dirk / 铁制短剑",
        "GalaxySword_Description": "It's unlike anything you've ever seen. / 谁与争锋。",
        "WindSpire_Name": "Wind Spire / 疾风利剑",
        "WoodMallet_Name": "Wood Mallet / 木锤",
        "DwarfHammer_Name": "Dwarf Hammer / 矮人锤",
        "Cutlass_Description": "A finely crafted blade. / 质量上乘的刀刃。",
        "DwarfSword_Name": "Dwarf Sword / 矮人剑",
        "HarveysMallet_Name": "Harvey's Mallet / 哈维的锤子",
        "AlexsBat_Description": "The sweet spot is dented from Alex's famous Grand Slam. / 亚历克斯赢得大满贯的棒球棍。",
        "CrystalDagger_Description": "The blade is made of purified quartz. / 此刀由纯石英打造。"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Strings/WorldMap",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "GingerIsland_East_JungleHut": "Jungle Hut / 丛林树屋",
        "GingerIsland_West_GourmandCave": "Gourmand Frog / 饕餮青蛙",
        "GingerIsland_West_BirdieShack": "Birdie's Shack / 贝啼的小屋",
        "GingerIsland_SouthEast_PirateCove": "Pirate Cove / 海盗湾",
        "GingerIsland_West_TigerSlimeGrove": "Tiger Slime Grove / 老虎史莱姆树林",
        "GingerIsland_South_Dock": "Willy's Boat / 威利的船",
        "GingerIsland_West_QiWalnutRoom": "Qi's Walnut Room / 齐先生的核桃房",
        "GingerIsland_West_Shipwreck": "Shipwreck / 沉船",
        "GingerIsland_North_DigSite": "Dig Site / 挖掘场",
        "GingerIsland_North_Volcano": "Volcano / 火山",
        "GingerIsland_North_FieldOffice": "Field Office / 办事处",
        "GingerIsland_West_House": "Island Farmhouse / 姜岛农舍",
        "GingerIsland_South_Resort": "Resort / 度假村",
        "GingerIsland_North_Trader": "Island Trader / 姜岛商人"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/Abigail",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "summer_Tue4": "You're an interesting ${guy^lady}$, @. I'm glad you moved here.$h / 你这人真有趣，@。你能搬来这里真是太好了。$h",
        "Resort_Entering": "I hope a mermaid visits the beach. / 我希望有美人鱼能光临海滩！",
        "Thu": "#$1 Abigail1#Oh no, I think my Dad's going to cook dinner tonight...$s / #$1 Abigail1#今天晚上估计要由我爸下厨了……$s#$e#I don't feel like doing anything today...$u / 我今天什么都不想干……$u",
        "summer_6": "I went to the beach last night, after dark... Sometimes you can see strange lights bobbing over the sea. / 我昨晚去了海边……有时能在海面上看到奇怪的光在晃动。#$e#Or maybe that was just a dream I had... It doesn't feel real anymore. / 或许那只是我做的一场梦……感觉不是很真实。",
        "summer_Thu": "If I knew how to use a sword I would be exploring those caves by the mountain lake right now. It's probably nice and cool in there. / 要是我知道怎么用剑，立马就会去湖边的山洞里探险。那里肯定漂亮极了。",
        "summer_Fri10": "Do you ever get lonely on your farm? / 你在农场会不会觉得孤单啊？",
        "Event_VideoGame_Yes": "Great! I'm sure you'll be able to beat this level with ease.$h / 非常好！我敢说你不费吹灰之力就能闯过这一关。$h",
        "fall_1": "Ah... Fall's here!$h / 啊……秋天来了！$h#$e#I was getting so tired of summer. / 我真是早就受够夏天了。",
        "fall_Tue": "$d joja#I try to help out in the shop on most days. Business has been pretty bad since the Joja Mart opened, though. / 我一般都会在店里帮忙。但自打 Joja 开业以来，生意就变得难做了。|Ever since Joja Mart shut down we've been doing great at the shop! / 自此 Joja 关门之后，我们店子的生意就变得特别红火了！$h",
        "Resort_Shore_2": "Hmm, you think I could sneak my guinea pig onto the island? / 唔，你觉得我能偷偷把我的豚鼠带到岛上来吗？#$e#Nah, David's probably not much of a swimmer anyways.$h / 啊不行，大卫应该不太会游泳。$h",
        "summer_10": "Everyone's excited for the Luau tomorrow. Maybe a little nervous, too, considering the Governor will be here. / 大家都翘首期盼明天的宴会呢。由于州长要来，或许气氛还会有一些紧张。",
        "Introduction": "Oh, that's right... I heard someone new was moving onto that old farm. / 啊，对了……我听说有人搬到那座旧农场。#$e#It's kind of a shame, really. I always enjoyed exploring those overgrown fields by myself.$9 / 说来还挺遗憾的呢，我一直都很喜欢一个人在那片杂草丛生的农田里探险。$9",
        "summer_Sat": "I'm looking forward to fall... the cool mountain breeze, the swirling red petals, the smell of mushrooms... *sigh* / 我期待秋天的来临……期待清爽的山风、飘摇的红色花瓣，还有蘑菇的香味……*唉*",
        "Sat6": "You came all this way to visit me? That's nice.$h / 你是专程来看我的吗？真贴心呢。$h#$e#So have you been exploring the mountain caves at all? / 这么说来，你去探索过那些山洞了？#$e#Interesting. I'd like to go there myself one of these days.$l / 有意思。我也想找个机会，独自去走上一趟。$l",
        "fall_Mon8": "You know, I could actually see myself becoming a farmer some day... / 我确实想过自己有一天会变成农夫……#$e#But how would that ever happen? *chuckle*$l / 但那一天什么时候才能到来呢？*轻笑*$l",
        "Mon": "Oh, hey. Taking a break from work? / 哦，嘿。你是在休息吗？",
        "movieTheater": "Did you hear about the new movie theater in town? I'm excited to check it out!$h / 镇上新开了一家电影院，你听说了吗？我超想去看看！$h",
        "summer_Thu4": "Ew, I hope I don't get a tan this summer.$s / 但愿我今年夏天别被晒黑才好。$s",
        "secondChance_Girls": "*sigh*... I can't stay mad at you anymore, @. Let's just move on with our lives.$s / *叹*……我不能再对你生气了，@。让我们往前看，继续生活。$s",
        "Event_Grave4": "Really? That's surprising.$8 / 真的？太不可思议了。$8#$b#I've lived in the valley my whole life, but I've never really done anything memorable. I want to go on an adventure!$8 / 我一辈子都住在山谷里，但从没做过一件值得纪念的事情。我想去闯荡一番！$8",
        "summer_1": "Summer's here. It's not really my favorite season. / 夏天来了。我可不喜欢这个季节。#$e#The air is so muggy I feel like I'm floating in soup. / 天气闷热，感觉自己就像被泡进了热汤里。",
        "Wed2": "Oh, hi @. Taking a break from your work? / 啊，你好啊，@。你是在休息吗？#$e#Me too. Oh! Nothing physical... just some online classes I'm taking. / 我也是。噢！我没干什么体力活……我刚才在上网络课程。",
        "FlowerDance_Decline": "That's flattering... but I'm gonna have to say no. Sorry. / 真是受宠若惊呢……但我还是得说不行。对不起了。",
        "winter_24": "I'm going to eat so much cranberry sauce tomorrow.$h / 我明天要吃一大堆蔓越莓酱。$h",
        "fall_Wed": "I can't wait to see some pumpkins this year.$h / 我等不及要见见今年的南瓜了。$h#$e#The spirit's eve festival happens at the end of the season. It's pretty low-key compared to what you'd see in Zuzu City, but for a small town like this it's a lot of fun. / 万灵节就安排在这个季末。虽然和你们在祖祖城里举行的活动没法儿比，但对我们这种小镇而言，已经算是很有意思的了。",
        "Fri2": "We're all going to hang out in the saloon this evening. It's kind of like a Friday tradition, I guess. / 今天晚上我们都要去酒吧玩。这大概算是周五的传统吧。",
        "Wed": "Hey. Sorry in advance if I say anything rude. I didn't get much sleep last night. / 嘿。要是我说了什么难听的话，请别介意。我昨天晚上没怎么睡着。#$e#What do you want? / 你有什么事吗？",
        "fall_Fri10": "I usually feel lonely this time of year, but not anymore.$l / 每年的这个时候我都会觉得孤单，但以后不会了。$l#$e#@, what are your plans for the future? / @，你对将来有什么打算吗？",
        "dumped_Girls": "Don't talk to me!$a / 不要跟我说话！$a",
        "eventSeen_2_memory_oneday": "Sebastian mentioned that he heard strange music while having dinner the other night... / 有天晚上吃饭的时候塞巴斯蒂安说他听到了奇怪的音乐……#$e#I didn't tell him it was us! It seemed better to keep it a mystery.$h / 我没告诉他是我们演奏的！神神秘秘的也挺好。$h",
        "summer_Thu10": "Wow, you look nice today. / 哇哦，你今天真漂亮。#$e#I mean, that summer air is really good for the complexion, isn't it?... heh...$l / 我是说，夏天的空气真的具有美颜效果呢，是吧？呵呵……$l",
        "Sun_Bad": "Rude! Why would you hurt my feelings like that? You're so insensitive!$s / 太无礼了！你怎么能这样伤害我的感情？你简直不可理喻！$s",
        "Event_Tragic_2": "...!$h / ……！$h",
        "Event_Cave2_2": "@... I'm alright.$8 / @……我没事儿。$8",
        "fall_Sat": "$d cc#I can't believe you fixed up that old Community Center all by yourself. I'm really impressed. / 你居然一个人就修好了那个破旧的社区中心？！我真是对你刮目相看呢。|Do you have any scarecrows on your farm? / 你的农场里有稻草人吗？",
        "fall_26": "Will I see you tomorrow at the Spirit's Eve festival? Look for me in the haunted maze.$h / 明天你会去万灵节庆典吗？去闹鬼迷宫找我吧。$h",
        "mineArea_10_oneday": "I heard you've been exploring the old mines. That sounds like fun!$h / 我听说你一直在探索旧矿井，感觉很有意思！$h#$e#...I'm working up the courage to go there myself...$s / ……我想鼓起勇气自己去看看……$s",
        "AcceptBirthdayGift_Positive": "Hey, you remembered my birthday... Thanks, @! This is really nice!$h / 欸，你还记得我的生日啊……谢谢你，@！我很喜欢这个！$h",
        "Event_Grave3": "Oh, it's because I'm a girl... isn't it? Ugh...$u / 哦，就因为我是个女孩儿……对不对？呃……$u^Why? I'm just as strong as you!$a / 怎么啦？我哪里不如你了！$a#$b#I'm not some fragile princess.. I can take care of myself!$a / 我不是娇滴滴的小公主……我能照顾自己！$a#$b#I've lived in the valley my whole life, but I've never really done anything memorable. I want to go on an adventure!$8 / 我一辈子都住在山谷里，但从没做过一件值得纪念的事情。我想去闯荡一番！$8",
        "winter_Fri": "One thing I've learned living here... everyone stares at you if you look different. / 在这里生活让我明白了一件事……如果你的外表与众不同，那所有人都会盯着你看。",
        "winter_Sun": "Oh, hello.#$q 29/30 winter_Sun_old#I made these two drawings. What do you think?#$r 29 20 Sun_29#I like the jungle island and the tiger.#$r 30 5 Sun_30#I like the orc with the battleaxe.#$r 29 -50 Sun_Bad#I don't like either of them. / 哦，你好啊。#$q 29/30 winter_Sun_old#我画了两幅画。你觉得怎么样？#$r 29 20 Sun_29#我喜欢丛林海岛和老虎这一幅。#$r 30 5 Sun_30#我喜欢拿着战斧的兽人这一幅。#$r 29 -50 Sun_Bad#我哪幅都不喜欢。",
        "GreenRain": "I want to go exploring, but I can tell my Mom is kind of worried. I don't want to add to her stress. / 我想去探险，但是我知道我妈有点担心。我不想增加她的负担。",
        "fall_Mon": "I need to stretch my legs and get some fresh air today. / 我今天得活动活动腿脚，呼吸一下新鲜空气。",
        "Sun_nothing": "You know, that wouldn't be so bad.$8 / 那倒也没什么好难过的。$8",
        "eventSeen_1_memory_oneweek": "Hey, I finally beat the first level of Journey Of The Prairie King! Watching you play helped a lot. / 哎，我终于打过《草原王者大冒险》的第一关了！看你玩了一局对我帮助很大。",
        "breakUp": "Oh... I... I understand. You see me as just a friend...$s / 哦……我……我明白了。你只是把我视作朋友……$s#$b#I guess we weren't really a good match...$s / 可能我们并不太合适……$s",
        "AcceptGift_(O)StardropTea": "Wow... the color is so beautiful, like an amethyst. Thanks! / 哇……这颜色太好看了，像紫水晶一样。谢谢你！",
        "Sun_WildColor": "You're always good for a laugh.$h / 你总是这么搞笑。$h",
        "winter_Sat6": "I've been daydreaming a lot lately... / 我最近一直在做白日梦……#$e#Oh! You want to know what it's about? Well...$u / 噢！你想知道我梦到的是什么吗？唔……$u#$b#...It's a secret.$h / ……那是个秘密。$h",
        "summer_Mon8": "I used to think Pelican Town was kinda drab, but lately I'm starting to love some things about it.$h / 我原以为鹈鹕镇是个枯燥乏味的地方，但我竟然慢慢爱上它了。$h",
        "Tue4": "Hi, I'm glad to see you.$h / 嗨，很高兴见到你。$h#$e#I want to take my mind off things for a while... how is your day going? / 我想稍稍换换脑子……你今天过得怎么样？",
        "summer_Tue": "The air is so thick with honey and nectar all summer. I almost feel dizzy.$u / 整个夏天，空气里都是蜂蜜和花粉的味道。搞得我一直晕乎乎的。$u",
        "Resort_Umbrella_3": "Hey @, you think you could build a raft? / 嘿，@，你觉得你能做个木筏出来吗？#$e#I saw a few cool islands on the way here I want to visit. / 我在来的路上看到了几个很酷的岛屿，我想去看看。",
        "Sun2": "I wonder what would happen if I spent all night in the graveyard?#$q 17/18 Sun_old#@, what do you think happens to us after we die?#$r 17 0 Sun_17#I have no idea.#$r 18 40 Sun_18#We come back as spooky ghosts.#$r 17 0 Sun_17#We go to Heaven.#$r 18 0 Sun_17#Our energy bodies enter the astral plane.#$r 17 30 Sun_nothing#Nothing. We just cease to exist. / 要是在墓地里待上一整夜会发生什么事呢？#$q 17/18 Sun_old#@你觉得我们死后会变成什么样？#$r 17 0 Sun_17#我不知道。#$r 18 40 Sun_18#我们会变成鬼魂。#$r 17 0 Sun_17#我们会上天堂。#$r 18 0 Sun_17#我们的能量体会进入灵界。#$r 17 30 Sun_nothing#什么都不会发生。我们就是不存在了而已。",
        "Event_Tragic_1": "Yeah... I guess my own life is okay...$s / 对……我想我自己的生活还好……$s",
        "summer_27": "You can't miss tomorrow's festival. It's one of the most beautiful wonders of the valley. / 你绝对不能错过明天的庆典。那是星露谷最美的盛景。",
        "dating_Sam": "Hey, I heard you and Sam got together... He's a really good guy!$h / 哎，我听说你和山姆在一起了……他人真的挺好的！$h#$e#We've been friends for a long time. You'd better be good to him, or you'll see my bad side! / 我们认识很久了，你最好对他好一点，不然我就对你不客气了！",
        "winter_Sat": "It's the weekend! / 到周末了！#$e#That means I can play twice as many video games.$h / 也就是说，我玩游戏的时间能翻倍啦。$h#$e#Bye. / 再见。",
        "eventSeen_733330_memory_oneday": "Sam and Sebastian asked me to play drums in their band... I've never played drums before, but it's actually pretty fun. / 山姆和塞巴斯蒂安邀请我去他们的乐队当鼓手……我从来没打过鼓，不过还挺有意思的。#$e#You have to learn how to move your limbs to different rhythms, at the same exact time. I feel like my brain is growing.$h / 你得学会让手脚同时跟上不同的节奏，我感觉大脑要进化了。$h",
        "summer_Sat6": "I'm actually enjoying myself this summer.$h / 我其实挺享受这个夏天的。$h#$e#It's funny how quickly one's outlook can change. / 人的观点居然能转变得这么快，真是奇妙。",
        "fall_Sat6": "Hi.$h / 嗨。$h#$e#Your hair looks cool today... did you do something different? / 今天你的头发好酷啊……你做了什么改变吗？",
        "FlowerDance_Accept": "Hey, sure. Let's do it. We can be embarrassed together.$h / 欸，好啊。我们一起跳吧，这样可以一起尴尬。$h",
        "dating_Abigail_memory_oneyear": "Uh... @? We've been dating for almost a year. Is this going anywhere?$s / 呃……@？我们在一起快一年了，未来怎么办？$s",
        "Thu10": "Hi.$l / 嗨。$l#$e#Do you feel like everything seems unreal lately?$l / 你有没有觉得，最近一切都没有真实感？$l#$b#Not in a bad way, though.$h / 但这样并没有什么不好。$h",
        "Resort_Shore": "The beach is okay, but it gets boring pretty quick. I'd rather check out that dark jungle, or the volcano! / 海滩还不错，但很快就玩腻了。我更想去看看那片黑暗的丛林，还有火山！",
        "Sun_old": "$p 17#I guess you think nothing would happen, right?$u / 你是不是认为什么都不会发生？$u|Maybe a wicked ghost would appear! / 也许祸乱人间的邪恶鬼魂就会出现啦！",
        "Resort_Umbrella_2": "Hey @, want to build a sand castle with me? / 嘿，@，想不想和我一起做个沙堡？#$e#Actually, a sand dungeon might be cooler!$h / 要是建个沙堡地牢就更酷了！$h",
        "Mon2": "Oh, hi! / 啊，嗨！#$e#Do you ever hang out at the cemetery? It's a peaceful place to spend some time alone. / 你去过墓园没？那里可是个独处的好地方呢。",
        "winter_1": "Well, fall is over...$s / 嗯，秋天过去了……$s#$e#But I like winter, too!$h / 但我也一样喜欢冬天！$h",
        "dating_Abigail": "%Abigail is blushing, but she looks happy. / %阿比盖尔脸红了，不过看起来很高兴。",
        "Resort_Umbrella": "My skin gets burnt really easily. So I'm just gonna stay under this umbrella for a while. / 我的皮肤很容易晒伤，所以我得在伞下待一会儿。#$e#I like it in the shade. Too much sun makes me dizzy. / 我喜欢阴凉处，被大太阳晒着会让我头昏脑涨。",
        "summer_Sun": "Do you ever get an urge to go exploring, @?#$q 25/26 summer_Sun_old#Okay... pretend you just won a free vacation. Where would you go?#$r 25 0 Sun_25#The beach#$r 26 30 Sun_26#In a dark cave#$r 26 30 Sun_26#The old, gnarled forest#$r 25 0 Sun_25#Joja Mega-Mall / 你有没有想去冒险的冲动啊，@？#$q 25/26 summer_Sun_old#好吧……假设你得到了一个带薪假期。你会去哪儿？#$r 25 0 Sun_25#海滩#$r 26 30 Sun_26#漆黑的山洞#$r 26 30 Sun_26#古老茂密的森林#$r 25 0 Sun_25#Joja 购物广场",
        "Sun_27": "I guess that's a pretty safe choice, huh? / 毕竟这样最保险嘛。#$e#I'll think about it. / 我会考虑一下的。",
        "wonEggHunt": "Feeling pretty good about the egg hunt, huh? Well, next year you won't be so lucky...$u / 昨天赢了心情很好是吧？呵呵，明年你运气就不会那么好了……$u",
        "Sun_30": "I'm glad. It's embarrassing to share your art with others. But I think you and I are on the same page. / 我很高兴。和别人分享自己的艺术作品是件挺难为情的事情。但我想咱俩的品位应该挺一致的。",
        "fall_Sun": "Hmm... what should I do tonight?#$q 27/28 fall_Sun_old#I was thinking about dyeing my hair again... what do you think?#$r 27 10 Sun_27#Dye it black.#$r 27 10 Sun_27#Why not blonde?#$r 27 20 Sun_WildColor#How about bubblegum pink?#$r 28 0 Sun_28#I like your hair just the way it is! / 嗯……今晚我该干些什么呢？#$q 27/28 fall_Sun_old#我想给我的头发重新染个色……你觉得什么颜色好？#$r 27 10 Sun_27#染成黑色吧。#$r 27 10 Sun_27#不妨试试金色吧？#$r 27 20 Sun_WildColor#粉红怎么样？#$r 28 0 Sun_28#我喜欢你现在的样子！",
        "winter_Thu": "Another year is almost over. / 这一年又要过去了。#$e#It goes by so fast, doesn't it?$s / 时间过得真快呢。$s",
        "AcceptGift_(TR)BasiliskPaw": "Disgusting... I love it!$h / 好恶心……不过我喜欢！$h",
        "Event_Rain_1": "I see...$8 / 原来如此……$8",
        "fall_Tue4": "I may fight with my parents a lot, but I know they're just looking out for me. They're doing what they think is best.$s / 虽然我经常和父母吵架，但我知道他们那是为我好。他们只是站在他们自己的立场上做了他们认为最好的事情。$s#$b#I dunno why I'm saying this to you. Don't tell anyone.$8 / 我也搞不懂为什么要和你说这个。不要告诉任何人。$8",
        "Resort_Leaving_2": "Maybe we'll see a sea monster on the way back. / 也许我们回去的路上会看到海怪。",
        "AcceptGift_(O)279": "Oh, wow... @! Are you sure you want to give this to me? It's so rare! / 哇……@！你确定要给我吗？这个太稀有了！#$b#I'll admit, my mouth is watering already...$h / 我承认，我已经开始馋了……$h",
        "winter_Thu10": "Another year is almost over... / 这一年又要过去了……#$b#But this was a really good year, don't you think?$h / 但你不觉得今年其实挺棒的吗？$h",
        "fall_Thu": "#$1 AbigailHAND#Last night I dreamt that my left hand had turned into a gigantic %noun. Does that mean anything? / #$1 AbigailHAND#昨天晚上，我梦到自己的左手变成了巨大的%noun。这难不成是什么预兆？#$e#%Abigail doesn't seem to be interested in talking right now. / %阿比盖尔这会儿似乎不想说话。",
        "GreenRain_2": "Have you seen all the crazy trees around town? Everything looks so different... I feel like we're in a fairy world. / 你看到镇上那些离谱的树了吗？变化真的好大……我感觉进入了童话世界。",
        "winter_Wed": "Hi. Is it boring to be a farmer during the winter? / 嗨。在冬天干农活是不是无聊透了？",
        "winter_Wed6": "It must be nice not having crops to worry about this time of year. / 每年到这个时候，就不需要操心庄稼了，真是太好了。#$e#And that means you can hang out with me more often!$h / 而那也意味着，你就有更多时间来找我玩啦！$h",
        "Tue2": "...*sigh*...$s / ……*唉*……$s#$e#I know my parents mean well, but sometimes they just cannot understand my point of view. Weren't they ever young? / 我知道我的父母是出于好意，但他们有时候就是不能理解我的想法。难道他们就没有年轻过吗？",
        "Resort": "Bummer... Willy says we have to stay on the beach...$s / 唉……威利说我们必须待在海滩上……$s#$b#And I brought my sword and everything...$s / 我都把我的剑和其他东西带来了……$s",
        "AcceptGift_(O)Book_Void": "Whoa, that's a creepy looking book... I love it! / 哇，这本书看着好吓人……我很喜欢！#$b#*Flip* *flip* *flip*... Ooh... It's full of monsters...$h / （翻、翻、翻）……哇……全是怪物……$h#$b#I'll have to study this before going into the caves... Thanks! / 进洞穴探险之前我得好好研究一下……谢谢你！",
        "Sun_28": "Of course that's what you'd say.$u / 你当然会这么说。$u",
        "Event_Tragic_3": "I would feel better if I could believe that... / 如果我能相信的话，可能会感觉好点儿……#$b#But I don't.$s / 但我并不相信。$s",
        "Sun_17": "Hmm, interesting... / 嗯，有意思……",
        "fall_Thu10": "I had an interesting dream last night, with you in it. / 我昨天晚上做了一个很有趣的梦，还梦到了你。#$e#It was a good dream.$h / 那真是个美梦。$h",
        "eventSeen_3": "The spirits have a mind of their own...$l / 精灵好像有自己的想法……$l",
        "summer_Wed2": "I would love to live in an old farmhouse like you. / 我想像你一样，住在旧农舍里。#$b#The creak of a floorboard, the slow plumes of dust whispering through the rafters... There's something special about an old building, isn't there? / 地板的嘎吱声，椽子间飘起的尘烟……老房子就是有些特别之处，对吧？",
        "winter_Tue": "Doesn't a steaming hot cup of cocoa sound good right now? / 这会儿要是能来一杯热气腾腾的可可，岂不是美滋滋？",
        "Sun_25": "Huh. I think that would get old fast. / 哼，估计很快就会过时吧。",
        "winter_7": "I'm looking forward to making a snow man tomorrow. / 我好期待明天堆雪人啊。",
        "winter_Tue4": "It's so cold, I wish we had a hot cup of cocoa to share.$h / 好冷啊，要是能来杯热可可就好了。$h",
        "GreenRainFinished": "And just like that, everything's back to normal. It's like magic!$h / 转眼间，一切都恢复成往常一样，简直跟变魔术一样！$h",
        "cc_Begin": "Don't tell anyone, but I snuck into the old community center last night... I think it's haunted! / 偷偷告诉你啊，我昨晚溜进了那个破社区中心……我觉得那里在闹鬼！",
        "Sun": "Oh man... I've been pushing off my homework all weekend. Looks like I'll be pulling another all-nighter...$s / 哎哟……一整个周末都没写作业。看来又要熬个通宵了……$s",
        "4": "Oh, hi. / 嗨。",
        "divorced": "What are you doing here? Just leave me alone!$a / 你在这干嘛？离我远点！$a",
        "fall_Wed2": "Are you growing pumpkins on your farm this year? / 你今年种南瓜了吗？#$e#Save one for me!$h / 帮我留一个吧！$h",
        "Fri6": "The birds were happily chirping today. They're too simple to understand the future. / 今天小鸟们叫得好欢啊。它们那么单纯，根本就不担心未来。#$e#It's better to be like them, isn't it? / 像它们那样也挺好的，对不对？",
        "Sun_26": "Yea! That sounds wonderful.$h / 对！听起来棒极了。$h",
        "Event_Cave2_1": "@...$8 / @……$8",
        "Mon8": "$query PLAYER_NPC_RELATIONSHIP current any married roommate#I remember when you first arrived in town, I was a little sad that those old woods would be turned into farmland. But now I'm really glad you moved here!$h|...Oh, @! Hi.$h / $query PLAYER_NPC_RELATIONSHIP current any married roommate#我还记得一开始你搬来镇上的时候，我想到那片树林要变成农田就有点难过，不过现在我觉得你搬来这里真好！$h|……哎，@！$h#$e#Want to hang out for a while? Here! Let me read your palm. *giggle*$h / 要玩一会儿吗？来！我来看看你的手相，嘻嘻。$h",
        "summer_Sun_old": "$p 25#I do... but you probably wouldn't like the places I'm thinking about... / 确实……但你可能不会喜欢我提到的地方……|Maybe we'll be neighbors someday. I think we both have similar, weird tastes.$h / 说不定哪天我们还能成为邻居呢。我觉得咱俩的品位挺像，都挺诡异的。$h",
        "summer_Fri": "I kind of wish I had a cat. Unfortunately, my Dad is allergic to pretty much everything. / 我挺想养只猫的。但不幸的是，我爸是超易过敏体质。",
        "AcceptGift_(O)SkillBook_4": "Hey, this is my favorite magazine! My Dad won't let me have a subscription, so I have to get it on the black market like this...$h / 哎，这是我最喜欢的杂志！我爸不让我订，所以我只好到私下里偷偷买……$h",
        "Event_Cave_2": "I guess when you have something to lose, it's normal to be afraid...$l / 如果你有不能失去的东西，会害怕也很正常……$l",
        "Event_Grave1": "See? You understand why I'm out here, then. / 可不是吗，现在你明白我为什么会在这里了吧？#$b#I've lived in the valley my whole life, but I've never really done anything memorable. I want to go on an adventure!$8 / 我一直都住在山谷里，但从没做过一件值得纪念的事情。我想去闯荡一番！$8",
        "Sun_18": "Well that's an interesting theory!$h / 嗯，这个说法有点意思！$h",
        "Event_Rain_2": "Yea... I guess you would be one to appreciate this somber ambience. / 啊……我就猜你会喜欢这种阴郁的气氛。",
        "dating_Abigail_memory_oneday": "...You're cute.$l / ……你真可爱。$l",
        "dating_Sebastian_memory_oneday": "I heard you and Sebastian started dating... I didn't realize you guys had a thing...$6 / 我听说你和塞巴斯蒂安在一起了……我没注意到你们俩凑在一块儿了……$6",
        "Tue": "Ugh... I'm not in a good mood right now.$s / 呃……我现在没那个心情。$s#$e#I said I'm not in a good mood... what do you want?$a / 我说了我没那个心情……你想干嘛啊？$a",
        "AcceptBirthdayGift_Negative": "Hey, you remembered my birthday... Thanks, @!$h / 欸，你还记得我的生日啊……谢谢你，@！$h#$b#Oh, it's, uh... *sniff*... what is it?$s / 呃，这个……（闻了一下）……这是什么东西？$s",
        "spring_23": "Well, tomorrow is the flower dance. Dancing is alright, but they make me wear this stupid white dress...$s / 明天就是花舞节了。跳舞倒是没问题，但他们总让我穿这条傻里傻气的白裙子……$s",
        "AcceptGift_(O)109": "Whoa... Where'd you find this? The workmanship is fascinating... / 哇……你是在哪里找到的？这做工太帅了……#$b#It's a little too rusty to use, but I'll add it to my collection. / 生锈这么严重，没法用了，我就收藏起来吧。",
        "FlowerDance_Accept_Spouse": "B... But... I wanted to dance with...$s / 但……但是……我理想的舞伴是……$s#$b#Just kidding! Of course I'm dancing with you. I love you.$h / 开个玩笑而已！我的舞伴当然是你啊，我爱你。$h",
        "AcceptGift_(O)119": "This makes you wonder... Thousands of years ago, there was probably a little purple-haired cavewoman who played this flute, just like me. / 我在想……几千年以前，会不会也有一个紫色头发的女原始人吹过这支笛子，就像我一样。#$b#...I'll have to wash it before pressing it to my lips, though.$h / ……那我吹之前还是得把它洗一下。$h",
        "Resort_Wander": "An island this big has got to be hiding some buried treasure. / 这么大的岛一定藏着什么宝贝。#$e#Quick, get me a shovel! / 快，给我把铲子！#$e#Relax, I'm just kidding.$h / 哈哈，我就开个玩笑。$h",
        "summer_Wed": "Have you decorated your house at all? That's what I'd be doing if I had a house. / 你装修房子了吗？要是我有房子，就会好好装修一番。",
        "wonEggHunt_memory_oneyear": "I'm still mad that you beat me at the egg hunt last year. You'd better start practicing... / 去年的彩蛋寻宝你赢了我，我现在还是很生气。你最好早点开始练习……",
        "Event_VideoGame_No": "Oh? *sigh*... I guess I'll never get past this level, then...$s / 哦？*唉* ……我倒觉得我永远也过不了这一关。$s",
        "Event_Rain_3": "...That's true.$8 / ……的确如此。$8",
        "summer_Mon": "My pet guinea pig, David, just hates this hot weather. He's fussy. / 我的宠物豚鼠大卫，就不喜欢闷热的天气。他好难养的。",
        "winter_Wed2": "Hi. If you're ever bored, you can always hang out in my room. / 嗨。如果你觉得无聊，随时可以去我的房间玩。#$e#As long as I'm not changing, of course! / 当然，我换衣服的时候除外。",
        "Wed4": "I can't trust a person who doesn't like animals... / 我不会信任不喜欢动物的人。#$e#Oh, don't worry! I know you're an animal lover!$h / 啊，别担心！我知道你很喜欢动物！$h",
        "Event_Cave_3": "...Um, okay. Sorry.$9 / ……呃，好吧。抱歉。$9",
        "winter_Fri10": "@, there's something I want to tell you... / @，我想和你说件事儿……#$e#It's just... um... well... your boots! They, uh...look really clean... *gulp* / 其实……那个……就是……你的靴子！看起来，呃……真挺干净的……*吞口水* ……#$e#That's all... *sigh*$s / 就这些……*唉*$s",
        "Event_Cave_1": "...okay.$8 / ……好吧。$8",
        "AcceptGift_(O)66": "$c 0.5#Wow... it's just my color! Thanks, @!$h#Thank you! This is my favorite stone. It's so pretty. / $c 0.5#哇……我最喜欢这个颜色了！@，谢谢你！$h#谢谢你！这是我最喜欢的石头，非常好看。",
        "spring_12": "I'm definitely going to enter the egg hunt tomorrow. Are you? / 我明天一定会去参加彩蛋大寻宝。你呢？",
        "Sat": "The fresh mountain air is nice on a day like this.$h / 在这样的日子里，吸上一口山里的新鲜空气，真是美啊。$h#$e#I wonder if the frogs will make an appearance soon. / 青蛙大概也很快就会活跃起来了。",
        "winter_Mon": "It's just too cold to go outside much. / 就是太冷了，不能一直在外面待着。#$e#But I do enjoy building a snowgoon.$h / 但我真的很喜欢喜欢堆雪怪呢。$h",
        "Fri": "Wow, I just realized it's Friday. $u / 哇哦，我才想起来今天是周五。$u#$e#Sometimes I totally lose track of time. / 有时候我真是过的稀里糊涂的。",
        "Sun_29": "Oh yeah? I guess that makes sense. / 是吗？意料之中呢。",
        "Resort_Leaving": "I'm gonna ask Willy if we can take the scenic route back. / 我得问问威利我们能不能走一条风景优美的路线回去。",
        "married_Sebastian": "Congratulations on the marriage. I guess this means Sebastian won't be moving to the city like he always talked about.$6 / 祝你新婚快乐。塞巴斯蒂安不是一直说要搬到城里嘛，这样一来他就不会去了。$6#$b#That'll be nice. I'd be kind of sad if I never saw him again. We've always been good friends.$6 / 就挺不错的。假如真见不到他了，我会很难过的，毕竟我们认识这么久了。$6",
        "Event_Grave2": "Sure. I don't want to kill anything, either. I just want to do a little exploring without risking my neck! / 当然。我也不想多做杀孽。我只想在不危及性命的前提下稍稍探个险！#$b#I've lived in the valley my whole life, but I've never really done anything memorable. I want to go on an adventure!$8 / 我一辈子都住在山谷里，但从没做过一件值得纪念的事情。我想去闯荡一番！$8",
        "Resort_Bar": "Gus made me a dark purple refresher, to match my hair. It tastes great!$h / 格斯给我做了一杯深紫色的提神饮料，跟我的头发颜色一样，味道好极了！$h",
        "fall_Fri6": "I wish the season lasted a little longer.$8 / 我希望这个季节能再长一些。$8#$e#When the wind really picks up, I almost feel like a kid again. / 等风一起，感觉自己又回到了童年呢。",
        "married_Sam": "Haha... I can't believe Sam is a married man, now. Who would've thought?$h / 哈哈……谁敢相信，山姆居然结婚了？$h#$e#Joking aside, I think he'll make a great father some day. / 说正经的，我觉得他以后能当一个好父亲。",
        "winter_Sun_old": "$p 29#Remember those drawings I showed you a while ago? I accidentally threw them away.$s / 还记得前段时间我给你看过的画吗？我不小心把它们扔掉了。$s|Remember that drawing I showed you with the orc? I entered it into an online contest and won 50g!$h / 还记得我给你看过的兽人画吗？我拿它参加了一场网上绘画比赛，还赢了 50 金呢！$h",
        "fall_Sun_old": "$p 27#I was going to dye my hair but then I decided against it. / 我一开始打算染发，但后来一想还是算了吧。|Yes? What is it? / 怎么了？有什么问题吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/Alex",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "Event_beach2": "Really? You must be some kind of weirdo.$a / 真的？你还真是个奇怪的家伙啊。$a#$b#Sorry. / 抱歉。",
        "Fri8": "Hi @. You look sporty today.$h / 嗨，@。你今天挺有运动气息的嘛。$h^Hey @. Did you do something different with your hair? Something keeps grabbing my attention.$h / 嘿，@。你换了发型吗？我感觉眼前一亮呢。$h",
        "Resort_Entering": "Finally, we're here! / 总算到了！",
        "AcceptGift_(O)107": "Now that's what I call an egg! Imagine the size of the omelet... / 这才算是个蛋嘛！做成煎蛋卷该有多大……",
        "winter_Tue_inlaw_Haley": "Oh, hey. How's the married life coming along?$9 / 哦，嘿。婚后生活怎么样？$9",
        "Resort_Towel_2": "Phew, it feels good to finally get these abs a little sunlight. / 哎呀，总算让这些腹肌出来见见太阳了。#$e#Kind of a shame to have them hidden away all the time back home. / 回家后一直把它们藏起来有点可惜。",
        "Thu": "The air's starting to warm up... I'm feeling pumped. / 天气热起来了……我感觉有些喘不过气。",
        "summer_Wed8": "You know, I actually wouldn't mind being a farmer... it seems a lot like playing sports, in a way. / 我其实不介意当农民……从某种意义上来说，这和当运动员是一回事。#$e#I like being outdoors and doing things with my hands. / 我喜欢在户外用自己的双手做些事情。",
        "summer_Thu": "Hey, you must be getting pretty strong working on that farm all day. / 嘿，整天在农场里干活儿，你一定变得很强壮吧。^Hey, you must be getting pretty fit working on that farm all day. / 嘿，整天在农场里干活儿，你肯定会变得很健美。#$e#Maybe you'll reach my level some day. Something to look forward to, huh? / 或许有一天你会达到我的水平。是不是很期待哦？#$e#Why do you have that look on your face? / 你脸上怎么带着那种表情？",
        "Resort_Towel_3": "When I go pro, I'll vacation on islands all around the world. / 等我成为职业选手，我要去世界各地的岛屿上度假。#$e#But for now, this place will do just fine!$h / 不过目前就在这个地方过过瘾吧！$h",
        "Event_books2": "Yeah, I guess you're right...$s / 嗯，你或许说得对……$s",
        "fall_1": "Sure, it's getting colder... But it's still warm enough for sports! / 天气确实开始变冷了……但不妨碍运动！#$e#That's all I care about. / 知道这一点就足够了。",
        "AcceptGift_Positive_category_egg": "$c 0.8#Hey, thanks. Eggs are great for bulking up.#*crack*... *sluuurp*... Mmmm. Now that's what I call a snack. / $c 0.8#哦！谢谢你，蛋白质可是增肌利器。#（敲开）（吸溜）……嗯，这才够意思嘛。",
        "Introduction": "Oh, hey. So you're the new guy, huh? Cool. / 哦，嘿。你就是那个新来的吧？不错不错。^Hey, you're the new girl, huh? I think we're going to get along great. I'm Alex. / 嘿，你就是新来的那个姑娘，是不是？我们一定会相处得很愉快的。我是亚力克斯。#$e#I'll see you around. / 回见。",
        "summer_Sat": "Mmmm... I smell a barbeque. / 嗯……我闻到了烧烤的味道。#$e#Damn I could go for a burger. / 该死，我得来个汉堡包。",
        "Mon": "Did you know I was an all-star quarterback in high school? It's true.$u / 你知道吗？我上高中的时候可是全明星四分卫哦。真的。$u#$e#See this little star on my jacket here? That proves it. / 看到我夹克上这颗小星星了吗？这就是证明。",
        "Tue6": "Nothing's better than an energetic day at the beach with your friends... right? / 和朋友们在海滩上度过愉快的一天，没有能比这美的事情了……我说的没错吧？",
        "summer_Thu4": "Hey, you look like you're getting into some good shape this summer! / 嘿，今年夏天你的身材变得好好哦！#$b#All that farm work is paying off, huh? / 在农场里流的那些汗都值了，对不对？",
        "Wed_01_02": "Yeah, some people just aren't made for sports. / 对，有些人天生就不是运动的料。",
        "summer_1": "Hey. Summer is definitely the best time of year. / 嘿。夏天绝对是一年中最棒的时节。#$e#Right now is great because we've got the whole season to look forward to. Catch you later. / 现在这个时间正好，可以憧憬整个夏天呢。回头见啦。",
        "summer_Mon4": "Hey, nice tan. / 嘿，肤色真不错。",
        "Resort_Wander_2": "I wonder if anyone would be up for a volleyball tournament. / 有人来排球比赛吗？#$e#Don't worry, I'll go easy!$h / 别担心，我会放水的！$h",
        "FlowerDance_Decline": "Nah... I'm gonna ask someone else. Good luck. / 算了……我去找别人问问。祝你好运。",
        "event_box4": "That doesn't make me feel any better, jerk.$a / 笨蛋，我一点都没感到安慰。$a",
        "AcceptGift_Negative_book_item": "Uhhh... Reading? Yeah, um... I guess I can give it a try.$s / 呃……要我读书？那什么……我或许可以试试。$s",
        "AcceptGift_(O)305": "Oh... um... I usually like eggs, but this one looks evil.$s / 啊……呃……我挺喜欢吃蛋的，可是这个看起来有点吓人。$s",
        "fall_Wed": "Hey, I want to ask you something. / 嘿，我想问你件事。^Hey, can I ask you something? / 嘿，我能问你件事吗？#$e#$q 54/55 fall_Wed_01_old#Do you think the ladies like my haircut? / $q 54/55 fall_Wed_01_old#你觉得女孩子会喜欢我的发型吗？^What do you think about my haircut?#$r 54 30 fall_Wed_01_01#It looks very fashionable.#$r 55 -30 fall_Wed_01_02#It looks like some kind of fungal growth. / 你觉得我的发型怎么样？#$r 54 30 fall_Wed_01_01#看起来挺时尚的。#$r 55 -30 fall_Wed_01_02#像头上长了蘑菇一样。",
        "purchasedAnimal_Chicken_memory_oneday": "Hey, I overheard someone saying that you got your first chicken the other day. / 哎，之前我无意中听说你买了一只小鸡。#$b#Man... I wish Grandma had chickens. I'd eat a dozen raw eggs for breakfast each morning! / 好家伙……要是外婆也养鸡就好了，那我每天早饭都要吃一堆生鸡蛋！",
        "Wed": "Looks like a good day to play catch, huh?$u / 今天挺适合打球的，对不对？$u#$e#$q 5/6 Wed_01_old#I'd ask you to throw the ball around, but you don't really seem like the sports type. / $q 5/6 Wed_01_old#我还想叫你一起投投球，但你好像不怎么喜欢运动。^If you weren't a girl I'd ask you to play catch.#$r 6 0 Wed_01_02#I'm fine just watching you from a distance.#$r 5 15 Wed_01_01#I want to play catch with you!#$r 5 0 Wed_01_03#(angry) What's that supposed to mean? / 如果你不是女孩子，我就约你打球了。#$r 6 0 Wed_01_02#我站在旁边看就好了。#$r 5 15 Wed_01_01#我想和你打球！#$r 5 0 Wed_01_03#（愤怒）你到底是什么意思？",
        "fall_Thu2": "What's up, @? / 怎么了，@？",
        "fall_Sat": "I think you can find salmon in the river this time of year. / 每年的这个时候，都能在河里捞到鲑鱼。#$e#At least that's what I heard. / 起码我听说是这样的。",
        "fall_Wed_01_old": "I put too much gel in my hair today. It kind of hurts. / 今天我头发上喷太多发胶了。有点疼。#$e#Don't touch it! / 别碰！#$e#...what? / ……什么？",
        "Resort_Chair": "Aren't you hot in that outfit? C'mon, man... It's the beach! / 你穿那套衣服不热吗？别吧兄弟……这可是在海滩上！^Aren't you hot in that outfit? You gotta get some ocean breeze goin'! / 你穿那套衣服不热吗？你得感受下海风吹拂的感觉！",
        "firstVisit_BathHouse_MensLocker_memory_oneday": "I saw you checking out the bath house the other day. Trying to get in shape? Heh. / 之前我在澡堂看见你了，你是不是在健身？哈哈。#$e#Uh... you didn't go poking around in my locker, did you?$9 / 呃……你没有翻我的储物柜吧？$9",
        "fishCaught_159": "Heard you caught some kind of rare fish? / 听说你钓到了一条稀有的鱼？#$b#I'm impressed. Your arms must be stronger than they look! *pinch* ... not bad!$h / 很厉害嘛，你的手臂肯定很强壮！（捏）……还不错哦！$h",
        "winter_Fri": "You came all the way through the snow to see me? / 你居然冒着风雪专程来看我？#$e#I guess that makes sense. / 嗯，挺合情合理的。",
        "summer_Fri6": "Sorry my room is so messy.$s / 抱歉，我的房间好乱。$s#$e#It's just hard to always remember to clean. I'm trying to get better, though. / 我老是忘了打扫。不过我以后也会尽量勤快点的。",
        "Wed_01_01": "Really? I guess I underestimated you. / 真的？看来我低估你了。#$b#My arm's a little sore, but maybe next time. / 我的胳膊有点儿酸，要不还是改日吧。",
        "AcceptGift_(TR)FrogEgg": "Umm... I know I'm pretty big on eggs... But this isn't what I meant...$s / 呃……我确实很喜欢吃蛋……可是这个蛋实在是……$s#$b#Oh well... Down the hatch! *gulp*$h / 行吧……一口闷！（咕嘟）$h",
        "Event_parents1": "That's an interesting thought... / 这个想法很有趣……",
        "winter_Sun": "Hey, the gridball game is on today! / 嘿，格球比赛就在今天！#$e#This might be my favorite day of the week. / 这可能是一周里面我最喜欢的一天。",
        "eventSeen_288847_memory_oneweek": "Hey... uh... @? I... feel a lot more 'at peace' after talking to you on the beach last week.$s / 哎……那个……@？呃……上周在海滩上跟你聊过之后，我心里轻松多了。$s#$b#Thanks for listening to me.$s / 谢谢你听我说那些。$s",
        "winter_Wed8": "You know what? I'm going to start reading a book! / 你知道吗？我要开始读书了！",
        "GreenRain": "What's going on out there? Any action? / 外面咋了？要做什么吗？#$e#I gotta stay here with my grandparents...$s / 我就跟外公外婆待在这里……$s",
        "summer_Wed_01_old": "$p 52#Hey, when I turn pro you can say you were my first \"fan\". Not bad, huh? / 嘿，等我成了职业选手，你就可以跟人说，你是我的第一位“粉丝”。是不是挺酷啊？|Hey, I've been practicing twice as hard so I can turn pro and prove you wrong. You just wait.$a / 嘿，我已经在加倍练习了，所以我一定会进入职业队，然后证明你错了。你就等着瞧吧。$a",
        "fall_Mon": "My grandma told me I should spend more time studying. / 奶奶说我应该在学习上多花些时间。#$e#I was like, '...Grams, don't fret. I'm turning pro!'$h / 我当时就想，“……奶奶，别替我操心了。我会变成职业选手的！”$h#$e#Studying is for nerds, anyway. / 毕竟，学习是书呆子的专利。",
        "breakUp": "You're giving me wha...?$7 / 你这是在给我啥……？$7#$b#*huff*... Got it. Alright... well, you've made your choice. You're not gonna see me begging.$a / 呼……我知道了。好吧……嗯，看来你已经决定好了。我不会赖着不走的。$a",
        "AcceptGift_(O)StardropTea": "Whoa... this is great. Thanks! / 哇……这个太棒了，谢谢你！",
        "winter_Sat6": "I guess it's interesting that some people are totally different than us, you know? / 有些与我们截然不同的人存在，这不挺好玩儿的吗？#$b#I don't always understand why others act the way they do, but that's fine. / 我搞不懂他们为什么会那样，但我并不介意。",
        "summer_Tue": "If my hair wasn't so popular with the ladies, I swear I'd shave it all off in a second. / 要是我的发型不受女孩子欢迎，我肯定会马上把它剃掉。#$e#*sigh*... Life can be tough. / *唉* ……生活艰辛啊。",
        "winter_Tue4_inlaw_Haley": "I'll admit... I was a little jealous when you and Haley got married. But, hey... It's a chance for me to learn something new about myself.$9 / 我承认……你和海莉结婚的时候我有点儿嫉妒。但是，哎……这也是一个我重新了解自己的机会。$9",
        "Sun2": "Hey, @. / 嘿，@。#$e#That's right, I remember your name. / 对，我记得你的名字。",
        "winter_Sat": "There's some weird people living in this town. / 镇子里住了一些怪人。#$e#...like that guy Sebastian. Why does he wear black all the time? / ……就像塞巴斯蒂安。为什么他总是穿黑色的衣服？#$e#I don't get it. / 真是搞不懂。",
        "FlowerDance_Accept": "You beat me to it! I was about to ask you...$h / 你怎么先说了！我刚想问你……$h#$e#I'll see you out there. / 咱们到时候见。",
        "winter_Fri4": "You came all the way through the snow to see me? / 你居然冒着风雪专程来看我？#$e#That's nice of you.$h / 你这人实在是太好了。$h",
        "Resort_Shore": "I wonder how far I could swim out, and still make it back? / 不知道一个来回我能游多远？#$e#I'm guessing at least a mile. / 我猜怎么着也得有个一英里。#$b#... Don't worry, I'm not going to try it.$h / ……别担心，我不会真去试的。$h",
        "summer_Wed_01_02": "Yeah, well I'm so good I'm not going to have to practice all that much.$u / 对，我这么棒，根本不需要练习那么久。$u",
        "AcceptGift_(TR)ParrotEgg": "Can you eat this?$s / 这个能吃吗？$s#$b#I guess there's only one way to find out... / 看来只有试试才能知道了……",
        "winter_1": "Winter is kind of lame. There's too much snow to do anything fun. / 冬天太无聊了。经常下雪，找不到有趣的事情。#$e#I guess some people like it. / 我猜有人喜欢冬天。",
        "summer_Sun": "I got these new shoes yesterday 'cuz my old pair had a brown smudge. / 我昨天买了这双鞋，因为原来那双粘了一块儿褐色的脏东西。#$b#I just threw them into the garbage. I would've donated them but I don't like the idea of some weirdo wearing my shoes, ya know? / 我直接把旧鞋扔进了垃圾堆。我原本可以把它捐了，但我怕被哪个神经病捡去穿，这你理解吧？#$e#...What?$a / ……什么？$a",
        "fall_Sun": "Hey, the gridball game is on today! / 嘿，格球比赛就在今天！#$e#Sundays are pretty awesome in the fall.$u / 秋天的周日最棒了。$u",
        "Sat10": "I've been having a hard time staying focused lately.$l / 我最近很难集中注意力。$l",
        "winter_Thu": "When I turn pro, I'll be so rich that I'll get a vacation home in the tropics. / 等我成为职业选手，挣了钱，就要在热带买个度假别墅。#$e#Then I won't have to deal with these boring winters. / 然后就不用再过这种无聊的冬天了。",
        "dating_Alex": "%Alex gives your arm a squeeze, grinning. / %亚历克斯咧嘴笑着，捏了一下你的手臂。",
        "AcceptBirthdayGift_Loved": "Aw yeah, that's the good stuff... Thanks for the birthday gift, @. / 太好了，我超喜欢这个东西……@，谢谢你送我生日礼物。",
        "Event_beach1": "Of course you do. If you didn't I'd think you were crazy. Or some kind of nerd. / 那是当然的了。不然我会以为你疯了。要不然就是傻了。",
        "AcceptGift_(O)928": "Hehe... Keep giving me these every day, and I'll be able to retire at thirty!$h / 嘻嘻……多送我点这个，我三十岁就能退休了！$h",
        "winter_Thu10": "If I ever make a lot of money, I'll make sure all my friends and family are taken care of. / 要是我能挣到大钱，一定会让我的亲朋好友过上好日子。#$e#That means you, too.$h / 也包括你在内。$h",
        "fall_Thu": "What's up? / 近来如何啊？#$e#Isn't your name, like, %firstnameletter%name, or something? / 你是不是叫……%firstnameletter%name呀？#$e#Oh. It's @? Okay. Sorry. / 噢。@？好。抱歉。",
        "GreenRain_2": "I tried to go for a run this morning, but the plants have gone crazy! I couldn't get very far... / 我早上想去晨跑，可是植物长疯了！所以就没跑多远……",
        "winter_Wed": "People stay indoors a lot during the winter, and do boring stuff.$s / 冬天，人们都会待在家里，做些无聊的琐事。$s#$e#Maybe if I read a book I'd be less bored... nah. / 或许看看书就不会那么无聊……才怪。",
        "Resort": "Ah... The island life. I could get used to this! / 啊……我会习惯岛屿上的生活的！",
        "married_Haley": "You got Haley to marry you, huh? I always figured she was out of your league! / 你居然跟海莉结婚了？我还以为你根本追不到她呢！",
        "summer_Wed_01_03": "That's insane. You're just jealous that I'm talented and popular and you're not.$a / 你有毛病吧。你就是看我比你有天赋，比你受欢迎，所以眼红了。$a^That's ridiculous. You're just jealous that I'm way more popular than you'll ever be, freak.$a / 怎么可能。你就是看我比你受欢迎得多，所以嫉妒了，你个神经病。$a#$e#Get away from me.$a / 离我远点儿。$a",
        "event_box2": "Wow... It's the anniversary of my Mom's death! Have a heart...$a / 呀……今天是我妈的忌日！你就发发慈悲吧……$a",
        "secondChance_Guys": "I don't know if I can trust you anymore, but I'm willing to give you a chance.$9 / 我不知道我是否还能相信你，但我愿意给你一次机会。$9",
        "cc_Bridge": "Have you been up by the lake recently? I was on a run late last night, and I noticed that the old bridge was repaired... / 你最近去过湖边吗？我昨晚深夜跑步的时候，发现那座断桥居然修好了……",
        "fall_Thu10": "@! Um... Hi.$l / @！呃……嗨。$l",
        "eventSeen_288847": "Uh... I'm not used to opening up like that...$s / 呃……我平时不太会那样倾诉的……$s",
        "Event_parents2": "They would never do that!$a / 他们不会那么做的！$a",
        "winter_Tue": "Hey, can you go find Haley and tell her I said 'hi'? / 嘿，你能不能代我去跟海莉问个好？",
        "winter_Tue4": "Hey, @. Could you do me a favor?$l / 嘿，@。你能帮我个忙吗？$l#$b#If you see Haley, tell her I'm busy.$l / 要是你见到了海莉，告诉她我正忙着呢。$l#$e#Thanks. / 谢谢你。",
        "summer_Sat10": "I've been trying to do more reading lately... I feel like I've been neglecting my brain for years because of my athletic obsession. / 我最近一直想多读读书……我感觉自己太沉迷于运动，脑子都快生锈了。",
        "Sun": "Hey. / 嘿。#$e#What, you wanna talk to me? I'm busy. / 怎么，有话要和我说吗？我这会儿正忙着呢。",
        "Event_parents3": "...Maybe you're right... I dunno.$s / ……或许你是对的……我不知道。$s",
        "dating_Alex_memory_oneday": "Well, this is a %season I'll never forget!$l / 唔，我永远不会忘记这个%season！$l",
        "fall_Wed8": "I finally took the plunge... I've decided to stop putting gel in my hair. / 我终于下定决心……不会在往头发上抹发胶了。#$e#I wouldn't want to be friends with someone who only liked me because I have gel in my hair. / 那些因为我抹了发胶才喜欢我的家伙，我可不想和他们做朋友。",
        "divorced": "I thought we had something special... I guess I was wrong.$s / 我还以为我们之间的关系很特殊……我可能是自作多情了。$s",
        "summer_Wed_01_01": "Hey, now that's what I'm talking about!$h / 嘿，我就是这个意思！$h#$e#You're cooler than I thought. / 你比我想象的还要酷。",
        "Event_books1": "No, I'm not! You're just trying to flatter me.$a / 我才不是呢！你这是在恭维我。$a",
        "fall_Wed_01_01": "Yeah, I know. That's why I have it like this. / 是啊，我知道。所以我才喜欢。",
        "Sun4": "Hey, @. / 嘿，@。#$e#How's your day going? / 今天过得怎么样？",
        "Mon8": "You know, I used to want fame and fortune, but lately I've been starting to sing a different tune. In the end it's the humble little things that satisfy, don't you think? / 我曾经想要追逐名利，但最近，我的想法发生了改变。到了最后，真正能让人满足的其实就是一些微不足道的小事，你说是不是？#$e#I still want to go pro, but it's not the most important thing in the world. / 我仍然想当职业选手，但那已经不是这个世界上最重要的事情了。",
        "winter_Thu6": "I wish I could control the weather. / 真希望我能控制天气。",
        "summer_Fri": "What do you want? / 有什么事吗？#$e#I've got more important things to do right now. / 我这会儿还有更重要的事情要做。",
        "fishCaught_139": "I saw you catch that salmon. / 我看见你钓到了一条鲑鱼。#$b#If you happen to make a 'salmon dinner' out of it, let me have a bite! / 如果你打算做“鲑鱼晚餐”，记得给我留一口！",
        "Fri4": "Hey, @. I'm glad you stopped by. / 嘿，@。很高兴你能来。#$e#I'm not ashamed to say that I love my grandma! / 我敢光明正大地说我爱我奶奶！#$e#Now Grandpa, on the other hand... / 至于我爷爷嘛……#$e#Just kidding.$h / 说笑呢。$h",
        "AcceptGift_(O)442": "Mmm... Duck egg... Rich and creamy. *crack*... *slurp*. Ahhhh... / 嗯……是鸭蛋……粘稠又细腻。（敲开）……（吸溜）……啊……",
        "AcceptGift_(O)289": "Whoaa... It's so heavy I could use it for bicep curls. I'll be slurping on this for a week! Hah hah!$h / 哇……这么重，都能用来练弯举了。这个我能吃上一个星期！哈哈！$h",
        "fall_Wed_01_02": "Yeah right. You're just jealous that I look so good. / 没错儿。看我这么帅，你就是眼红了。",
        "Tue": "The beach is a cool place to hang out and soak up some rays. / 海滩是个值得一玩的好地方，在那里还能做个日光浴。#$e#You gotta spend some time in the sun or else you'll get all pale. / 你得时常晒晒太阳，要不然肤色就会变得苍白。#$e#*sigh*... I wish there were more girls in this town, know what I mean?$s / *唉* ……真希望镇上能多些女孩子，你明白我的意思吧？$s^Hey, do you wanna hang out with me at the beach some time? Do you have a bikini? / 嘿，有空跟我去海滩玩玩啊？你有比基尼泳衣吗？",
        "AcceptBirthdayGift_Negative": "What the...? Uh, I dunno what it's like where you grew up, but to me, this is trash.$a / 什么鬼……？呃，不知道你老家那边觉得这个怎么样，对我来说这就是垃圾。$a",
        "FlowerDance_Accept_Spouse": "Okay, this should be fun... I hope I can remember the moves this year! It's been a while...$h / 好吧，这应该会很有趣……希望今年我能记住舞步！有好长时间没跳舞了……$h",
        "Event_books3": "You were supposed to disagree with me.$a / 你应该反对我才对。$a",
        "summer_Sun4": "Oh wow...your shoes are a little dirty... but that's fine, too! / 哦……你的鞋有点儿脏……但也没关系！#$e#Different people have different tastes I guess. / 每个人品位都不一样嘛。",
        "event_box1": "Yes... I know. That's why I've been so determined to be successful with my sports stuff...$9 / 对……我知道。所以我才下定决心，一定要在运动生涯中取得成功……$9#$b#Make it or not... As long as I try my hardest I think she'd be proud. Thanks. / 不管成功与否……只要尽了全力，我想她都会以我为傲。谢谢你。",
        "Resort_Wander": "I knew I shoulda brought a frisbee... Oh well.$h / 好吧，早知道应该带个飞盘来的……$h",
        "summer_Wed": "Hey farm guy, I've got a question for you. / 嘿，农家小伙儿，我有个问题想问你。^Hey Farm girl, I've got a question for you. / 嘿，农家女孩儿，我有个问题想问你。#$b#$q 52/53 summer_Wed_01_old#Do you think I'll ever turn pro?#$r 52 30 summer_Wed_01_01#You're destined to be a sports legend#$r 52 0 summer_Wed_01_02#Maybe, if you practice a lot#$r 53 -50 summer_Wed_01_03#No, you'll most likely fail and become a salesman / $q 52/53 summer_Wed_01_old#你觉得我能成为职业选手吗？#$r 52 30 summer_Wed_01_01#你一定会成为运动场上的传奇#$r 52 0 summer_Wed_01_02#可能吧，你毕竟练习了那么久#$r 53 -50 summer_Wed_01_03#别做梦了，你还是老老实实去做推销员吧",
        "Resort_Towel": "With this island open, there's no excuse to be pasty anymore! / 现在岛屿开放了，可就没有借口继续宅在家里了！",
        "fall_Mon4": "My grandma told me I should spend more time studying. / 奶奶说我应该在学习上多花些时间。#$e#Maybe she's right...$s / 或许她是对的……$s",
        "Wed_01_03": "Uh... never mind. / 啊……算了。",
        "summer_Mon": "Hey, farmer guy. You look a little burnt. / 嘿，农家小伙儿。你怎么一副被烤焦的样子？^Hey Farmer girl. You've got a nice tan going.$h / 嘿，农家女孩儿。你的皮肤晒得挺不错啊。$h#$e#The more I practice this summer, the easier it'll be for me to go pro. / 今年夏天我练得越多，进入职业队的把握就越大。#$e#Then you'd be able to say you knew me once. Cool, huh? / 然后你就可以和人说你认识我了。很酷吧？",
        "fall_Fri": "I'm going to do two hundred sit-ups tonight. / 我今晚要做两百个仰卧起坐。#$b#I'm pretty dedicated, aren't I?$h / 我是不是很努力啊？$h#$e#Need anything else? / 你还需要什么吗？",
        "AcceptGift_(O)Book_Defense": "Aw, yeah... I've been looking for this one. It's supposed to be full of tips for bulking up. Rule number one... Eat a ton of eggs! Hah, no problem! Thanks!$h / 哇，太好了……我一直在找这本书，读完之后肯定能练成铜墙铁壁。第一条……要多吃蛋！哈，不成问题！谢谢你！$h",
        "Wed_01_old": "#$p 5#Go long! ...just kidding. Hahaha.|I just wish I had someone to play catch with...$s / #$p 5#长途奔袭！……开个玩笑而已。哈哈哈。|我只想找个人一起玩球……$s",
        "AcceptGift_(O)403": "*crunch*... Mmm... Nuts. That hits the spot. Thanks, @! / （嘎嘣）……嗯……有坚果，我可喜欢了。@，谢谢你！",
        "Sat": "My arms are really sore, but that's the sign of progress for a guy like me. / 我的胳膊好酸啊，但对我这样的人来说，这正是取得进步的标志。#$e#I must've done a thousand push-ups yesterday. / 我昨天肯定做了一千个俯卧撑。",
        "winter_Mon": "You like the snow? Me... I'm just looking forward to spring. / 你喜欢下雪吗？我……我一心只期盼着春天。",
        "Fri": "Hey, what's up farmer guy? / 嘿，怎么啦，农家小伙儿？^Hey, it's farm girl. Did you get new pants? You're doing something right. / 嘿，原来是农家姑娘啊。你穿了新裤子吗？这就对了。#$e#Oh, I almost forgot! It's my day for doing push-ups! / 哦，差点忘了。今天是我做俯卧撑的日子！#$e#Every time I do push-ups I try to do one more than last time. Pretty cool strategy, huh? / 每次我做俯卧撑，都会试着比上次多做几个。这种锻炼方法挺棒的吧？",
        "Resort_Leaving": "Aw... I guess it can't last forever.$s / 啊……快乐的时光总是这么短暂。$s",
        "event_box3": "...Thanks, @. / ……谢谢你，@。#$b#You... you're different than the other guys. More sensitive.$l / 你和别人不一样。你的心思更加细腻。$l^You've become my best friend in the whole town...  / 你是我在整个镇上最好的朋友……#$b#I'm glad. / 我很高兴。^Is that embarrassing to say?$l / 这种话很难启齿吗？$l",
        "Resort_Bar": "I'm ordering a banana shake with two scoops of protein powder. / 我点了一份香蕉奶昔加两勺蛋白粉。",
        "fall_Fri6": "I'm going to do a ton of sit-ups tonight. / 我今晚要做一万个仰卧起坐。#$e#You have to work really hard if you want to achieve your maximum potential. / 如果想要最大限度地发挥出潜能，就得努力拼搏。",
        "dumped_Guys": "You're not worth my time.$a / 不要浪费我的时间。$a"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/Caroline",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "GreenRain_2": "Ah, the special rain is back! This year, I'm going to make the most of it! / 啊，特别的雨水又来了！今年我要大展身手！#$e#This calls for a cup of green tea!$h / 先来一杯绿茶！$h",
        "married_Abigail": "I'm so happy for you two! Welcome to the family!$h / 我真为你们俩高兴！欢迎加入这个家庭！$h",
        "winter_Wed6": "Are you excited for the new year? / 是不是迫不及待要迎接新的一年了？#$e#I predict that you'll be super-successful on your farm.$h / 我相信你的农场一定会超成功的。$h",
        "Resort_Entering": "Willy gave us each a piece of his fish jerky. I'm still chewing on it. / 威利给每个人分了一块鱼干。我还在啃呢。",
        "Resort": "Hi @. Are you here to relax, or to do work? / 你好啊，@。你来这里是为了放松还是干活？",
        "Thu": "#$1 Caroline1#Hmmm... I wonder if I can get Pierre to cook dinner tonight. / #$1 Caroline1#嗯……不知能不能让皮埃尔负责今天的晚饭。#$e#Hmmm... what am I going to make for dinner tonight? / 嗯……今天的晚饭我该做些什么好呢？#$e#Maybe I'll just get take-out from the Saloon. / 要不从沙龙那儿买份儿外卖好了。",
        "fall_Mon_inlaw_Abigail": "Abby was taking online classes here, but I don't think her heart was really in it... / 阿比盖尔曾在这里上网络课程，但我觉得她的心思并不在那上面……#$e#She's a free spirit, like I was before I met Pierre. She's probably having the time of her life on your farm. / 她是个独立又要强的孩子，就像我遇到皮埃尔之前那样。她可能是想在你的农场生活。",
        "fall_Tue": "I've seen edible mushrooms in the forest. / 我在森林里见到了可以吃的蘑菇。#$e#Foraging can be a fun way to earn some cash. Or you can use what you find as gifts or food. / 采集山货是挣钱的好方法。你也可以把你找到的东西当作礼物送人或者自己留着吃了。",
        "Introduction": "Hello! You must be @, the new farmer. I'm Caroline. / 你好！你就是那个新来的农民，叫@吧？我是卡洛琳。#$e#My husband runs the general store here. And have you met my daughter, Abigail? She's the pale one with the purple hair. / 我丈夫在这儿开了个杂货店。你见过我的女儿阿比盖尔吧？她很白暂，一头紫发。",
        "summer_Sat": "Is it just me, or does Abigail look a little pale? / 阿比盖尔是不是脸色不太好？#$e#Maybe I'm just worrying about her too much. / 也许是我太担心了。",
        "Sat6": "#$1 Caroline12#When we first moved here, I took a while to settle down... I wasn't ready for the domestic life. / #$1 Caroline12#我们刚搬到这里的时候，我花了些功夫才安顿下来……我对于家庭生活还没有做好准备。#$e#Pierre's a bit conventional... but he's a good man. He's ambitious, but he always puts his family first. / 皮埃尔有点儿传统……但他是个好人。他也有雄心壮志，但他总把家庭放在第一位。",
        "Mon": "I wish Abby wouldn't spend so much time in her room. / 我希望阿比盖尔别总待在她的房间里。",
        "summer_Wed6": "Time seems to go by faster and faster the older you get...$s / 长大后，你就更容易理解什么叫时光飞逝，日月如梭了……$s",
        "winter_Tue": "Winter is harsh, but you can dig up some roots if you're lucky. / 冬天的生活很艰难，不过幸运的话还是可以挖到一些植物的根。#$e#Foraging can be a fun way to earn some cash. Or you can use what you find as gifts or food. / 采集山货是挣钱的好方法。你也可以把你找到的东西当作礼物送人或者自己留着吃了。",
        "AcceptGift_(O)16": "Oh, you've been foraging! Thank you! / 哦，你在采集是吧！谢谢你！#$b#I'll make a spicy cocktail sauce with this. That'll put some hair on Pierre's chest.$h / 我就用这个做一个辣的蘸酱，皮埃尔吃了肯定会觉得精神百倍。$h",
        "Sun": "Today I'm just going to relax and think positively. / 今天我要放松一下，各种烦恼放下，过一天积极的生活。#$e#Do you ever take a day off? / 你给自己放过假吗？",
        "Wed": "Hi there. Do you have everything you need for the farm? / 嗨。你农场里的东西都置办齐了吗？#$e#If not, we might be able to help you out. / 如果还缺什么的话，尽管来找我们帮忙。#$e#We carry a variety of useful items. / 我们什么好东西都有。",
        "Mon_inlaw_Abigail": "Hi, @. Are you enjoying the married life? I hope so! / 嗨，@。结婚了开心吗？希望如此！",
        "fall_Sat": "Is it just me, or does Abigail play too many video games? / 难道只有我觉得阿比盖尔玩游戏玩得太多了吗？#$e#Maybe I'm a little old-fashioned. / 也许我太落伍了。",
        "houseUpgrade_1": "$y 'I heard you got a new kitchen! Think you'll be doing a lot of cooking?_I plan to!_It's a good skill to have. And with all those fresh ingredients on your farm, you'll be sitting pretty!_Nah, it's just for looks_I see. Well, don't forget to eat right... nutrition is important.' / $y '我听说你有了个新厨房！你会经常做饭吗？_我正有此意！_会做饭可是很实用的，你还有农场上的新鲜食材，条件可谓是得天独厚！_没有，只是撑个门面。_好吧，不过还是要健康膳食……营养是很重要的。'",
        "AcceptBirthdayGift_Positive": "Thanks, sweetie. That's very kind of you to remember my birthday.$h / 谢谢你，亲爱的，你能记得我生日真是太好了。$h",
        "Resort_Chair": "%Caroline is trying to nap. / %卡洛琳想打个盹。",
        "Mon8": "#$1 Caroline23#When we first moved to Pelican Town I would take secret walks to the Wizard's tower. Don't tell Pierre, he has jealousy issues. / #$1 Caroline23#我们刚搬到鹈鹕镇的时候，我有时会悄悄溜达到法师塔那里去。别告诉皮埃尔，他这人心胸狭窄。#$e#Abigail was born about a year after we moved to Pelican Town. I wonder if she'll ever experience life outside the valley? / 我们搬到鹈鹕镇一年后，阿比盖尔就出生了。不知道她有没有机会去看看谷外的生活呢？",
        "married_memory_oneweek": "Ah, the newlywed. So, how was the honeymoon? / 哎呀，新婚夫妇，你们蜜月怎么样？#$e#I see. Well, I guess the farm would wither if you took time away... / 这样啊，好吧，我想如果你们离开太久，农场上的作物确实都要枯萎了……",
        "movieTheater_memory_oneweek": "It's fun to have a movie theater in town. I want to go see a western! / 镇上有个电影院真不错，我想去看西部片！",
        "winter_Fri": "Even though it's cold, I still check on the public garden beds every now and then. / 虽然现在天气很冷了，可我还是会时不时地去检查下公共花园。#$e#I just want to make sure they aren't damaged too much before spring returns. / 我这么做只是为了让它们在春天到来之前不会凋零。",
        "GreenRain": "I've never seen green rain before... It must not be too dangerous if you made it here! / 我第一次见到绿色的雨……你能安全到这里来，看来不是特别危险！",
        "fall_Mon": "Fall is Abby's favorite season, so I'm hoping she'll come out of her room more often. / 秋天可是阿比盖尔最喜欢的季节啊，正因为如此我希望她可以从屋里出来，多在外面待会儿。",
        "dating_Abigail_memory_oneday": "Abby told me that you and her are seeing each other. That's sweet! / 我听阿比说你们在一起了，真好啊！",
        "achievement_15": "Judging by the savory smells wafting from your place, I can tell you've been busy in the kitchen!$h / 你家总是飘来香味，我想你在厨房忙得不亦乐乎吧！$h",
        "Tue": "I've seen wild horseradish in the forest. / 我在树林里见过野生山葵。#$e#Foraging can be a fun way to earn some cash. Or you can use what you find as gifts or food. / 采集山货是挣钱的好方法。你也可以把你找到的东西当作礼物送人或者自己留着吃了。",
        "AcceptGift_(O)StardropTea": "Ooohh... this is nice. I'll save it for a quiet day in the sunroom. / 哦哦……这个太棒了，我要在日光房安安静静地坐着喝。",
        "AcceptBirthdayGift_Negative": "Oh... is that... a birthday gift? I see... well, thanks for stopping by.$a / 呃……这个是……生日礼物？哦……好的，谢谢你过来。$a",
        "summer_Sat_inlaw_Abigail": "How's Abigail's health? She's always been such a pale girl. Hopefully the farm lifestyle puts a little color in her cheeks. / 阿比盖尔的身体怎么样？她脸色一直很苍白。希望农场生活能让她脸颊红润起来。",
        "summer_Tue": "I've been seeing wild fruits in the forest lately. / 我最近在森林里见过野果。#$e#Foraging can be a fun way to earn some cash. Or you can use what you find as gifts or food. / 采集山货是挣钱的好方法。你也可以把你找到的东西当作礼物送人或者自己留着吃了。",
        "winter_Sat": "Don't you think Abby would look better with her natural hair color? / 不觉得阿比盖尔发色自然的时候更好看吗？#$e#She used to have light chestnut-colored hair. / 她的头发之前是浅栗色的。",
        "summer_Wed": "Hi there. Do you have everything you need for the farm? / 嗨。你农场里的东西都置办齐了吗？#$e#If not, we might be able to help you out. / 如果还缺什么的话，尽管来找我们帮忙。#$e#We carry a variety of useful items. / 我们什么好东西都有。",
        "cropMatured_815": "I noticed you're growing tea on your farm. Make sure to bring me a cup!$h / 我看到你在农场里种了茶叶，记得给我带一点啊！$h",
        "Sat2": "Abby's always had a strange interest in the occult. I'm not sure where she gets it from... / 阿比盖尔对怪力乱神有着诡异的兴趣。我不知道她是从哪儿学来的这些玩意儿……",
        "Resort_Shore": "The water is so warm here compared to the valley. It's really pleasant! / 与山谷里相比，这里的水很暖和。太开心了！",
        "eventSeen_719926": "Are you feeling relaxed? I bet... / 你觉得放松了吗？我觉得肯定是……",
        "fall_Wed6": "You know, I used to want to be a farmer myself. Well, more like a rancher. / 我以前还想务农呢。好吧，其实我更想当一名牛仔。#$e#I always loved movies about the wild west when I was a girl. / 我还是个小女孩的时候可是非常喜欢西部电影的。",
        "wonGrange": "Pierre's trying to play it cool, but he's seething about losing to you at the Stardew Valley Fair. / 皮埃尔之前在星露谷集市上输给你，他装作不在意，其实还耿耿于怀呢。",
        "Sat4": "Abby's always had a strange interest in the occult. I'm sure it's just a phase... / 阿比盖尔对怪力乱神有着诡异的兴趣。我不知道她是从哪儿学来的这些玩意儿……",
        "summer_Mon": "On Wednesdays the shop is closed. / 周三的时候商店不开门哦。#$e#Keep that in mind if you're going to need anything. / 如果要买东西的话，可一定要牢记啊。",
        "summer_Sun": "Today I'm just going to relax and think positively. / 今天我要放松一下，各种烦恼放下，过一天积极的生活。#$e#Do you ever take a day off? / 你给自己放过假吗？",
        "Wed6": "Stardew Valley is nice, but I wish I knew more people. / 星露谷是个好地方，不过我还是喜欢多认识些人。#$e#I'm glad that we've become friends. / 很高兴我们可以成为朋友。",
        "Sat": "Is it just me, or does Abigail have an unhealthy interest in doom and gloom? / 难道只有我觉得阿比盖尔对毁灭和黑暗有着畸形的兴趣吗？#$e#Maybe I'm just too old to understand. / 或许是我年龄大了，理解不了她们了。",
        "Fri": "It's a fine-looking day. / 今天天气真不错呢。#$e#On days like this I like to help Evelyn with the public gardens. / 在这样的日子里，我喜欢去帮艾芙琳照料公共花园。#$e#She's strong for her age, but I think she appreciates all the help she can get. / 以她的年龄来说，她挺能干的，但她也肯定也乐于接受别人的帮助。",
        "Sat_inlaw_Abigail": "Dinner's been a lot quieter since Abigail moved out... / 自从阿比盖尔搬出去后晚饭时间就安静了很多……#$e#No, not because she used to chew with her mouth open!$h / 不，不是因为她以前总是吧唧嘴！$h",
        "Resort_Leaving": "I'll sleep well tonight!$h / 我今晚会睡得很好！$h",
        "Resort_Bar": "I told Gus to surprise me, and he made an iced green tea with mango zest. How nice!$h / 我让格斯给我个惊喜，然后他做了一杯芒果皮冰绿茶。这太棒了！$h"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/Clint",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "GreenRain_2": "I feel bad admitting it, but sometimes I wish there was a real disaster, not just some dumb green rain. / 有时候我真希望来一场货真价实的天灾，而不是这个破绿雨——我知道这想法很糟糕。#$b#Something to shake everything up, you know? / 得是那种，惊天动地级别的。#$b#Not that I want people to get hurt... / 我不是想要有人受伤……#$b#I just want to feel alive... To feel like I have a purpose... / 我只是想要有活着的感觉……有人生的目标……",
        "Fri8": "I should save up and buy a computer... / 我应该攒钱买台电脑……#$e#Maybe I can find a girlfriend on the 'internet'...$s / 在“互联网”上说不定能找到女朋友……$s#$e#What? Don't judge me! Not everyone is a cool, attractive, socially-adept farmer, you know!$u / 什么？你别看不起我！又不是所有人都长得帅，有魅力，善于社交，还有自己的农场的！$u#$e#What's a guy like me supposed to do? *Groan*$s / 我这种人到底要咋办啊？哎哟……$s",
        "Resort_Entering": "I'm gonna put on my special red trunks. They're supposed to be really eye-catching. / 我要穿上我的特制红色短裤，应该非常吸引眼球。",
        "Resort": "*sigh*... We're all at the beach but I still feel so alone...$s / 唉……大家都来沙滩上了，但我还是感觉很孤独……$s",
        "Thu": "Business has been slow lately. / 最近生意很冷清啊。#$e#You should upgrade your tools. I could use the cash. / 你该升级下你的工具了。这样我也能挣一笔。",
        "married_Emily": "%Clint is looking at the ground and won't say anything to you. / %克林特眼睛往下看，不肯跟你说话。",
        "Resort_Shore_2": "I thought working a furnace would have prepared me for this heat, but I'm sweating in places I didn't know I could.$s / 我以为跟熔炉打交道会让我适应高温，但现在我身上到处都在流汗。$s#$e#I hope no one noticed... / 我希望没人注意到……#$e#%Clint's body is glistening... / %克林特的身体正在闪闪发亮……",
        "Introduction": "Er... hi. I'm Clint. / 呃……嗨。我是克林特。#$e#I'm the town blacksmith. If you ever need to upgrade your tools, I'm your guy. / 我是这个小镇的铁匠。要是想升级农具的话，就来找我吧。",
        "Mon_rude": "Wow. That was rude. I was just being funny and you took it to a whole new level. / 喔。这样可很无礼哦。我不过是想开个玩笑罢了，你却把这件事搞严重了。",
        "Sat6": "Damn it, I'm too old to do anything exciting anymore. All I have to look forward to is years and years of sweaty, hot furnace-work. / 该死，我这岁数已经没法再做什么刺激的事情了。我能做的只剩下在这灼热的铁炉边上大汗淋漓地干铁匠活了。",
        "Mon": "Yep. I'm a blacksmith. / 没错。我是个铁匠。#$e#My father was also a blacksmith. / 我父亲以前也是一名铁匠。#$e#My grandfather was a blacksmith as well.$u#$q 9/9 Mon_old#I bet you can't guess what my great-grandfather was...#$r 9 30 Mon_9#A blacksmith.#$r 9 50 Mon_clown#A silly clown.#$r 9 -50 Mon_rude#A sarcastic jerk. / 我的祖父也是一名铁匠。$u#$q 9/9 Mon_old#你一定猜不到我的曾祖父以前是一名……#$r 9 30 Mon_9#铁匠。#$r 9 50 Mon_clown#一个糊涂的小丑#$r 9 -50 Mon_rude#一个尖酸刻薄的混蛋。",
        "event_advice1": "Okay... I'll keep that in mind. / 好吧……我记着点。",
        "GreenRainFinished": "Well that was a dud. And here I thought it was finally my chance to be a hero. Oh well... Back to the grindstone. / 雷声大雨点小啊，我还以为总算能当一回英雄了。唉……继续干活吧。",
        "mineArea_40": "Ah, I can tell from the scratch marks on your pickaxe that you've reached a deeper layer of the mines. / 啊，看你镐头上的划痕，想必你已经到过矿井深层了。#$e#If it starts getting difficult to break stones, you'll want to upgrade your pickaxe. I can help. / 如果石头越来越难敲碎，建议你升级一下镐头，我可以帮你。",
        "reject_868": "Hmm... That's an interesting stone, like nothing I've ever seen before. / 唔……那块石头很有意思，跟我以前见到过的完全不一样。#$b#I wouldn't know what to do with it, though. I deal in the mundane, not the magical... / 我不知道该怎么处理，毕竟我做的是平凡生意，不懂这些有魔法的……",
        "Sun": "Don't you have work to do? / 你没活干吗？",
        "Mon_9": "How'd you know?$u / 你怎么知道的？$u",
        "Wed": "Hey. What do you need? / 嘿。要点什么？",
        "divorced_Emily": "I've been feeling strangely hopeful lately. / 最近我莫名感觉自己有点希望。",
        "AcceptGift_(O)SkillBook_3": "Oh, interesting... These books aren't very easy to come by in the valley. / 嗯，很有意思……这书在星露谷可不容易弄到。#$b#Looks like there's a lot of good tips in here. Thanks, @. / 里面好像有很多实用的建议，谢谢你，@。",
        "Sun4": "So how are your tools holding up? / 你的那些工具现在用得怎么样？",
        "event_advice2": "That's the problem... I do act natural... but I never have any success.$s / 问题就在这儿……虽然我表现得很自然……可我从没体验过成功的感觉啊。$s",
        "AcceptBirthdayGift_Positive": "I don't usually get birthday gifts. This actually means a lot, @. Thank you. / 一般不会有人送我生日礼物。@，我很感动，谢谢你。",
        "Resort_Chair": "Ow... my whole torso is burnt to a crisp.$s / 嗷……我感觉我的身体都要被烤酥了。$s",
        "Mon8": "I hate to say it, but sometimes I'm glad my father forced me to become a blacksmith. At least I have a profession. / 我不得不承认，有时候我还挺庆幸我父亲当初逼我当铁匠，现在我至少有一份生计。#$e#If I didn't have work to do, I'd probably spend all day just sitting around feeling sorry for myself.$s / 假如我连可以干的活都没有，我大概只好整天无所事事，不停地感到后悔。$s",
        "Sun8": "I don't know if people realize this, or care, but I do take a lot of pride in my work. / 我其实对自己的工作很自豪，不过可能没人意识到，也没人在意。#$e#I mean... When I was a boy I didn't really dream of becoming a blacksmith. But that's what I am. And I want to be the best blacksmith I can be. / 我跟你说……我小时候的梦想不是当铁匠，可是现在我成为铁匠了，而且我想当最好的铁匠。",
        "GreenRain": "It's situations like this where a person's true character is put to the test. / 这种情况才是真正考验一个人有没有勇气。#$e#I'll keep Em... I mean, I'll keep everyone safe from the toxic rain! / 我会保护艾……那什么，我会保护大家不要淋到有毒的雨水！",
        "Tue": "If you want me to upgrade your tools you'll have to give me the correct ore. / 如果你想找我升级工具的话，就得给我找来合适的矿石。#$e#And you'll have to pay me a fee, of course. / 当然了，也得付我些钱啊。",
        "AcceptGift_(O)StardropTea": "You're giving this... to me? I don't think I deserve it, but.. thank you. / 这个是……要送给我的？实在是太贵重了……谢谢你。",
        "AcceptBirthdayGift_Negative": "Is this a birthday gift? It's, uh... an interesting choice. Well I appreciate that you remembered me, anyway. / 是给我的生日礼物吗？这个，呃……很耐人寻味，不过你能记得，我还是很感激。",
        "dating_Emily": "I... um... heard that you and Emily are together. Congratulations.$s / 呃……我听说你跟艾米丽在一起了，恭喜你。$s",
        "Mon_clown": "Hahahaha. Good one.$h / 哈哈哈。猜得好。$h",
        "Mon_old": "And yes, my great-grandfather was also a blacksmith. / 没错。我的曾祖父也是名铁匠。",
        "cc_Minecart": "Somehow, the old town minecart system started working again. It's very convenient for getting to and from the mines. / 不知怎的，旧城的矿车系统又开始运作了。对于往返矿山来说，这十分便利。#$b#Don't get too cozy, though... if it can start up so suddenly, it could just as well shut down... / 但是不是很舒服……如果它可以突然启用，它也会突然关闭……",
        "Resort_Shore": "Oh no... I forgot to clip my toenails.$s / 哎呀……我忘了剪脚趾甲了。$s",
        "Mon4": "Be glad you're a farmer, @. It's nicer to work outdoors than by a hot furnace all day. / 真羡慕你是个农民啊，@。在户外工作可比整天在热腾腾的大火炉旁边好多了。#$e#I'm only a blacksmith because my father pushed me into it. / 我当这个铁匠都是因为我爸爸非要让我当啊。",
        "eventSeen_101_memory_oneweek": "Did Emily say anything about our date the other day? / 艾米丽有提到我们前几天的约会吗？#$b#Wait, don't tell me... I'm better off not knowing. Maybe I can still salvage my dignity.$s / 等等，还是别说了……我还是不要知道了，这样还能挽回一点尊严。$s",
        "mineArea_121": "Interesting. There's tiny iridium flakes on your pickaxe... you've been going to the desert caves, huh? / 有意思，你的镐头上有铱矿石的碎屑……你是不是去了沙漠的洞穴？#$e#I've always wanted to smelt with iridium. It's not easy to come by. / 我一直想要用铱来熔炼，可惜不容易弄到。",
        "Wed6": "Oh, hi @. Sorry If I look a little messy. I've been working at the furnace all morning.$h / 啊，你好，@。真抱歉，我身上有点脏。我一整个早晨都在这个火炉边上工作。$h#$e#So, did you need anything, or do you just want to visit? / 话说回来，你有什么需要呢，还是只是来看看？",
        "Thu8": "I heard Emily has a friend who lives in the desert. Do you know anything about her? / 我听说艾米丽有一个朋友住在沙漠，你了解她吗？#$e#I wonder if she's single...$s / 不知道她是不是单身呢……$s",
        "Sat": "Sometimes I wonder how I ended up in this town.$u / 有时候我还会想想我在这个小镇最终会怎么样。$u",
        "Sat10": "How are your tools holding up? / 你的工具状态怎么样？#$b#If they ever need repairs, just come by my shop. I guarantee these tools for life! / 如果需要修理的话，直接来我店里，我给你终身保修！",
        "Fri": "The weather doesn't really matter to me. I typically stay near my shop year-round. / 这天气对我来说倒不是什么大问题。通常来说我一整年都在店附近转悠。#$e#Depressing, huh? / 听起来有点憋屈吧？",
        "Resort_Leaving": "Well, that didn't turn out like I was imagining... / 嗯，结果跟我想的不太一样……",
        "Resort_Bar": "I'm hungry...$s / 我饿了……$s"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/Demetrius",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "fall_Thu": "How's the farming business going? It's corn season, isn't it? / 你的农活干得怎么样了？到了种玉米的季节了，对不对？#$e#I can imagine it being pretty peaceful, working outdoors with plants all day. / 整日在户外工作一定相当恬静淡泊吧。",
        "GreenRain_2": "The rain appears to be harmless, so I'm taking less precaution this year. / 这场雨似乎是无害的，所以今年就不用那么小心翼翼了。",
        "winter_Wed": "Do you have a kitchen in your house yet? / 你家有厨房吗？#$e#Cooking is kind of like doing lab work. / 料理其实跟做实验挺像的哦。",
        "Resort_Entering": "I already spotted a rare crab. This place is great.$h / 我找到了一只稀有的螃蟹。这地方太棒了。$h",
        "AcceptGift_(O)107": "Wow, an intact dinosaur egg! This is an extremely rare specimen. Now, if only it could be incubated... / 哇，这是完好无缺的恐龙蛋！这个标本可是极其罕见，要是能孵化出来的话……",
        "Resort": "Can you believe this place? It's teeming with exotic life! / 这里到处是奇妙的生物，太令人难以置信了！",
        "Thu": "How's the farming business going? It's parsnip season, isn't it? / 你的农活干得怎么样了？现在是不是到了种防风草的季节了？#$e#I can imagine it being pretty peaceful, working outdoors with plants all day. / 整日在户外工作一定相当恬静淡泊吧。",
        "summer_Thu": "How's the farming business going? It's tomato season, isn't it? / 你的农活干得怎么样了？到了种西红柿的季节了，对不对？#$e#I can imagine it being pretty peaceful, working outdoors with plants all day. / 整日在户外工作一定相当恬静淡泊吧。",
        "fall_Tue": "We know a lot about nature thanks to science. / 多亏了科学我们才能对自然有这么多的了解。#$e#But there's always a lot more to learn. / 不过学无止境啊。",
        "Introduction": "Greetings! I'm Demetrius, local scientist and father. Thanks for introducing yourself! / 你好啊！我是德米特里厄斯，是这里的科学家以及神父。谢谢你的自我介绍！#$e#I'm studying the local plants and animals from my home laboratory. / 我在家里的实验室里研究当地的动植物。#$b#Have you met my daughter Maru? She's interested to meet you. / 你看到我的女儿玛鲁了吗？她很想见见你。",
        "summer_Mon6": "I became a scientist because I wanted to contribute to the progression of our species. / 我之所以要成为科学家，是因为我想帮助到我们这个物种的发展。#$e#Of course, none of this would be possible without farmers such as yourself.$h / 当然了，这一切都离不开像你这样的农民的帮助。$h",
        "summer_Sat": "Hmm... If strigolactone levels could be increased, would it have a proportional effect on mycorrhizal growth?$u / 嗯……如果独角金内酯的水平可以提高，会对菌根生长产生影响吗？$u#$b#Oh! Sorry. I was pondering some data and I didn't notice you there. / 噢！抱歉。我在思考一些数据，没注意到你。#$e#Do you need anything? / 有什么事吗？",
        "eventSeen_65_memory_oneweek": "$y 'How's that cave experiment coming along? Has it produced anything of value yet?_Yes_Ah! That means the conditions must be more suitable than I originally theorized... hmm..._No_Well, keep checking on it every now and then. I'm sure those little guys will yield something eventually.' / $y '洞穴的研究有没有进展？产生有用的东西了吗？_有_哦！说明那里的条件比我推测的还要合适……唔……_没有_那你经常去检查一下吧，最终肯定会产出一些东西的。'",
        "reject_869": "It's a good specimen, but a very common species. You can keep it. / 这是个很好的标本，不过只是常见的品种。你可以留着。",
        "Mon": "Maru helps me out in the lab sometimes... She's a good kid. / 玛鲁有时也会在实验室里帮我一把……她真是个好孩子。",
        "Event_tomato1": "Really? I figured a farmer would know the correct answer...$s / 真的？我以为农民会知道正确答案呢……$s",
        "winter_Tue": "Talk to my wife if you want to increase the size of your house. / 要是你想扩建房子的话可以和我妻子聊聊。",
        "Event_Lab_Rat": "*sigh*... %fork$4 / *唉*……%fork$4",
        "purchasedAnimal_Dinosaur": "Say that again!? You successfully incubated a dinosaur egg? This is unprecedented!$5 / 我没听错吧？！你成功孵化了恐龙蛋？简直是史无前例！$5#$e#Here, take my coffee, I'm all worked up now... I can't drink any more. [253] / 来，这杯咖啡就给你了，我现在兴奋得不得了……不能再喝了。[253]",
        "Sun": "It's good to take a break from work every now and then. / 时不时歇一歇是有好处的。#$e#I guess that's kind of difficult when you live on a farm, though. / 虽然我猜住在农场应该没什么休息的时间吧。#$e#Hey, at least in the winter you don't have to worry about crops. / 对了，至少在冬天的时候你不用操心那些作物啊。",
        "Wed": "You're probably growing a lot of interesting plants on your farm, huh? / 你现在一定是越来越对你的农场里的作物感兴趣了吧？#$e#Maybe I'll stop by your place some day and check it out. / 有机会我也许会到你那里去拜访一下呢。",
        "Event_tomato2": "See? @ agrees with me. / 看见没？@和我达成一致了哦。",
        "married_Maru": "*sigh*... @, I've come to accept that it's time for my 'little girl' to become a woman. You have my blessing.$s / 唉……@啊，我家的小女孩长成了大姑娘，我已经接受了，你们要好好的。$s",
        "fall_Sat": "Let's see... perhaps the nitrogen fixation level is affected by nematode secretions...$u / 唔……固氮水平也许是受线虫分泌物所影响的……$u#$b#Oh! Sorry. I was pondering some data and I didn't notice you there. / 噢！抱歉。我在思考一些数据，没注意到你。#$e#Do you need anything? / 有什么事吗？",
        "AcceptBirthdayGift_Positive": "A present!... with optimal timing. Today is the anniversary of my birth. Thank you!$h / 是礼物！……送的时机恰到好处，今天可是我出生的纪念日，谢谢你！$h",
        "Resort_Chair": "Are you having fun, @? You need to remember to take breaks now and then too! / @，你玩得开心吗？累了的话，记得休息一下！",
        "winter_Fri": "Hello. / 你好。#$e#%Demetrius seems lost in thought. / %德米特里厄斯好像陷入了沉思。",
        "summer_Fri": "$p 40#So I heard Maru had you look through that telescope out back. / 我听说玛鲁让你用了后面那个望远镜。|If you and Maru become friends, I'm sure she'll show you how to use that telescope out back. / 如果你和玛鲁成为朋友的话，我相信她一定会教你怎么用后面那个望远镜的。#$e#Pretty exciting, huh? / 很刺激啊，是不是？",
        "Fri4": "Robin has a hot temper. It's better to stay on her good side. / 罗宾可是个暴脾气。最好还是多说些她的好话吧。#$e#...now if I could only quantify her mood levels, perhaps I could model the fluctuations using a sinusoidal curve...$u / 如果可以划定她愤怒等级的话，我就可以用正弦波动模型建模了……$u",
        "winter_Sun": "Feel free to harvest as much lumber and stone from this area as you please. / 我这里的石头和木材都随便拿。",
        "questComplete_104_memory_oneday": "Checking up on the melon research? Yes, I... uh... 'analyzed' it, and it certainly has an optimal macronutrient profile... / 你想问甜瓜研究的事情是吧？我……呃……我“分析”过了，它的宏量营养素含量确实恰到好处……",
        "GreenRain": "Don't mind me, @. I'm just collecting some samples. This may be a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity!$7 / @，不用管我，我就采集一些样本。这可是千载难逢的机会啊！$7#$e#Erm... If you see my wife, can you tell her I'm okay?$7 / 呃……如果你遇到我老婆，麻烦你跟她说我没事。$7",
        "fall_Mon": "During this time of year I divert my attentions to fungi. / 这一整年我关注的重点都在真菌上。",
        "summer_Fri_inlaw_Maru": "I hope my daughter's keeping up on her math and science! / 我希望我女儿跟上数学和科学两门功课！",
        "Tue": "This valley has a very vibrant and diverse ecosystem. That's one reason I was excited to move here. / 星露谷这里有着非常活跃而多样的生态系统。正因为如此，我才迫不及待地搬到这里。",
        "AcceptBirthdayGift_Negative": "A present!... with optimal timing. Today is the anniversary of my birth.$h / 是礼物！……送的时机恰到好处，今天可是我出生的纪念日。$h#$b#Let's see what it is... $h / 我来拆开看看……$h#$b#...Oh.$s / ……啊。$s",
        "AcceptGift_(O)StardropTea": "Wow, this is a rare substance. I'll have to take it to the lab for... uh... further analysis. / 哇，这可是罕见的物质，我得带回实验室……呃……进一步分析。",
        "eventSeen_65_memory_twoweeks": "Don't forget to check that farm cave! There's bound to be something useful in there by now. / 别忘了去看农场洞穴！肯定已经出现有用的东西了。",
        "summer_Tue": "Make sure to water your plants every day. / 一定要每天给植物浇水。#$e#Although, if you're using water retaining soil you don't need to worry about watering as often. / 不过呢，要是你用的是保水肥料的话就不用太频繁地浇水了。#$e#It's pretty convenient. / 很方便吧？",
        "winter_Sat": "Let's see... if seasonal nitrogen levels could be modeled by a piecewise function...$u / 唔……如果季节性含氮量水平可以采用分段函数建模……$u#$b#Oh! Sorry. I was analyzing data and I didn't notice you there. / 噢！抱歉。我正在分析数据，没看到你。#$e#Do you need anything? / 有什么事吗？",
        "reject_865": "Fruit and salt? What an odd combination...$s / 水果加盐？好奇怪的搭配……$s",
        "fall_Fri_inlaw_Maru": "I'm still flabbergasted about Maru's secret robot... was it all a dream? / 我仍然对玛鲁的秘密机器人感到吃惊……难道都是梦吗？",
        "winter_Fri4": "Thanks for stopping by. I need to think about something other than legumes for a while. / 谢谢你来看我。我也不能光想着豆科植物了，得换换脑子。#$e#So, what have you been doing lately? / 你最近在忙什么？#$e#That sounds interesting. / 听起来很有趣啊。",
        "Resort_Shore": "*crunch*... whoops, there goes an endangered crab species...$s / （嘎吱）……哎呀，这种螃蟹要濒临灭绝了……$s#$b#... / ……#$b#Oh, never mind. It was just the empty shell! I can sleep tonight. / 哦，只是个空壳子，那没事了！我今晚能安心睡了。",
        "fall_Wed6": "Hi @. I'm always glad when you come for a visit. / 嗨，@。我时刻都欢迎你的到来。#$e#It's nice to have some company after all this lonely lab-work. / 要知道，一个人做实验无聊得很，能有人陪陪我真是太好了。",
        "summer_Mon": "#$e#%Demetrius is deep in thought. / %德米特里厄斯陷入了沉思。#$e#Sorry, I'm really busy. / 抱歉啊，我现在真的很忙。#$e#There's so many plants to study right now. / 我现在还有很多的植物要去研究呢。",
        "fall_Fri": "Maru sure spends a lot of time working on those gadgets of hers. / 玛鲁真是花了很多时间在她的那些小玩意上面。#$e#I'm glad she's so dedicated. / 看到她这么投入我很高兴。",
        "Wed6": "Hi @! How are you doing today? / 嗨，@！今天感觉如何啊？#$e#I wish I could make your farming job easier somehow. / 希望我可以帮你把农活变得更轻松些啊。",
        "pamHouseUpgradeAnonymous": "Robin won't even tell *me* who paid for Pam's new house! / 罗宾甚至不会告诉*我*谁为潘姆买了新房子！#$e#I pretend I'm mad at her but secretly I'm glad she's so loyal to her word...$h / 虽然我假装在生她的气，但偷偷地说，我很高兴她说到做到……$h",
        "Sat": "Let's see... If compounds in the rhizosphere contain sufficient levels of Carbon-13, then...$u / 唔……如果根际化合物的碳-13 水平足够的话……$u#$b#Oh! Sorry. I was pondering some data and I didn't notice you there. / 噢！抱歉。我在想数据的事，没注意到你。#$e#Do you need anything? / 有什么事吗？",
        "winter_Mon": "I'm taking a break from my research right now. / 我现在要休息一会儿。",
        "dating_Maru": "Yes, Maru told me the news. I can't say I'm thrilled about it, but maybe you'll prove me wrong.$u / 嗯，玛鲁告诉我了，我不算太高兴，不过希望你能让我刮目相看。$u",
        "winter_Thu": "Do you have any animals on your farm? / 你的农场养动物了吗？",
        "Fri": "Robin has a hot temper. It's better to stay on her good side. / 罗宾可是个暴脾气。最好还是多说些她的好话吧。#$e#Don't tell her I said that.$h / 别让她知道是我说的哦。$h",
        "Event_Lab_Silence": "Well, we'd better titrate this solution before it crystallizes on us. / 好吧，我们最好在结晶前滴定这个溶液。",
        "Resort_Leaving": "I'll be analyzing this data for months. / 我会花几个月的时间分析这些数据。",
        "firstVisit_Desert": "I heard you visited Calico Desert recently. How fascinating! I'm sure you observed many unique life forms on your trip. / 听说你最近去了卡利科沙漠，好有意思！你在旅途中肯定看到了许多独特的生物吧。",
        "married_Sebastian": "Congratulations on the marriage. Robin's been crying since the wedding. 'Tears of joy', as she calls it! A most peculiar concept... / 祝你们新婚快乐。婚礼之后罗宾一直在哭，她还说是那是太高兴了！真是古怪……#$e#Hmm, now that the basement is unoccupied, I might have to expand the laboratory...$u / 唔，既然地下室没人住了，我是不是可以扩建一下实验室……$u",
        "Mon_inlaw_Maru": "It's hard to do good science without Maru's help... / 没有玛鲁的帮助，想做好科研很难……#$b#But her happiness is much more important than my experiment! / 但是她的幸福比我的实验更加重要！",
        "Resort_Bar": "I usually don't partake... but I'm usually not on a tropical island, either. Hahaha.$h / 我一般不喝酒……但我一般也不会到热带岛屿上来。哈哈哈。$h"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/Dwarf",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "GreenRain": "I can't see the color green very well. / 我不太能分辨出绿色。#$b#I guess it's part of living underground for so long. / 可能是因为在地下待久了。",
        "firstVisit_IslandNorth": "If you enter the volcano on Ginger Island, you might encounter others like me. Don't be alarmed! We're peaceful with humans. / 如果你进入姜岛上的火山，可能会遇到我们族的人，不用惊慌！我们对人类很友好。",
        "Thu": "You're not a spy sent by the Shadow People, are you? / 你不会是暗影人派来的间谍吧？#$e#I'm keeping my eye on you. / 我可盯着你呢。",
        "Tue": "Ah... cave carrot stew, cave carrot roast, cave carrot soup and cave carrots au gratin. / 啊……煮山洞萝卜、烤山洞萝卜、山洞萝卜汤还有焗山洞萝卜。#$e#...And a ramekin of cave carrot brulee to sweeten the night. / ……还有让夜晚变得甜蜜的山洞萝卜布丁蛋糕#$e#What? / 什么？",
        "AcceptGift_(O)StardropTea": "*sniff*... is this milk? *sip*... hmm... tastes good. / （闻了一下）……这是牛奶吗？（喝了一口）……唔……挺好喝。",
        "AcceptBirthdayGift_Negative": "Oh! I've read about this tradition... it's a 'birthday gift', isn't it? / 啊！我在书上看到过这个传统……这个是“生日礼物”吧？#$b#So, is it part of the tradition to give out garbage like this? / 所以送别人垃圾也是一个传统？",
        "Introduction": "Hey, you're pretty good at mining, for a human. / 嘿，你身为一个人类，还真是擅长采矿啊。",
        "firstVisit_Caldera": "You found the legendary Dwarvish Forge? Incredible... I've never seen it, myself. / 你找到传说中的矮人锻造台了？太牛了……我自己都没见过。#$e#The machinery is so old, none of my people understand how it works. But it's definitely Dwarvish technology. / 那个机器太古老了，我们族已经没有人能理解它的原理了，不过能确定是矮人的技术。",
        "fishCaught_161": "Oh, you caught an Ice Pip? They're energetic little fish, despite the frigid environment they live in. My people avoid the frozen areas, though... too cold! / 哦？你钓到冰柱鱼了？这种小鱼生活在严寒的环境，但很有活力。我们族是不会去那种地方的……太冷了！",
        "Mon": "I got all this stuff from the surface. I just take it from your people during the night. / 这些东西都是地上捡的。就是晚上从你们那里拿来的。#$e#Hmm? What is this concept you call \"private property\"? / 嗯？你说的\"私人财产\"是什么？",
        "Wed_6": "Long ago, my people knew the secrets of advanced technology. The archaeological evidence proves that. / 很久以前，人们就知道了先进技术的秘密。考古学上的证据可以证明这一点。#$e#But I wonder where it came from? And where did it all go? I guess some questions will never be answered... / 可是我搞不懂这些知识人们都是从何处得来的？又产生了什么成果？我觉得有些问题可能永远没有答案……",
        "fishCaught_162": "Oh, you caught a Lava Eel? Very good! Lava Eel fishing is a big part of our culture. They're considered a delicacy! / 哦？你钓到岩浆鳗鱼了？很好啊！我们族也有钓岩浆鳗鱼的传统，这种鱼很好吃！",
        "Sun": "One day you'll have to tell me about this beverage you call \"milk\". / 有机会你得告诉我这个被你称为“牛奶”的饮料的一切啊。",
        "mineArea_121": "You know, you're pretty good at mining, for a human. / 我跟你说，你作为一个人类，采矿技术已经很强了。",
        "Wed": "Hey, wanna buy something? / 嘿，要买点什么吗？",
        "Sat_8": "The mines can be a treacherous place. Be careful, friend. / 矿井可是个危险的地方。小心啊，朋友。",
        "fishCaught_158": "Oh, you caught a Stonefish? I know them very well. We sometimes keep them as pets. / 哦？你钓到了石头鱼了？我很熟悉的，我们有时候会把它们当宠物养。",
        "Sat": "It's dangerous in the mines. Why don't you buy a few things from my shop to ensure your safety? / 矿井里很危险啊。不如在我的店里买点东西确保安全吧？",
        "Fri_2": "Most humans fear the unknown... that's why I've hidden my shop here. / 人们都对未知的事物感到恐惧……那就是为什么我要把店藏在这里。#$e#Your mining skills prove you're trustworthy. / 你的开采技巧已经证明你值得我的信任了。",
        "Thu_4": "I feel most comfortable underground. / 在地下感觉最舒服了。#$e#The deeper underground the better. / 越深越好啊。",
        "AcceptBirthdayGift_Positive": "Oh! I've read about this tradition... it's a 'birthday gift', isn't it? Hmm, very interesting... / 啊！我在书上看到过这个传统……这个是“生日礼物”吧？唔，很有意思……",
        "Fri": "You've never seen a dwarf before, have you? / 你以前没见过矮子吗？",
        "AcceptGift_Neutral_milk_item": "Ah, 'milk'... *slurp*... How interesting. Remind me, again... where exactly does this juice come from? / 啊，是“牛奶”……（哧溜）……真有趣。我又忘了……这个饮料是从哪里来的？#$b#...!!! *sploosh* / ……！！！（稀里哗啦）"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/Elliott",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "Fri8": "I'll admit... it takes me several hours each morning to make my hair look this good. / 我承认……每天早上我都会花几个小时来把发型弄好。",
        "event_toast1": "Well...okay. / 好啦……好啦。#$b#Here's to @! / 敬@！干杯！",
        "Resort_Entering": "That was quite the ride! / 好远啊！",
        "Thu": "Hello, @. / 您好，@。#$e#Are you well? / 你最近好吗？",
        "summer_Thu": "Oh dear! My shoes are filled with sand.$s / 啊啊！我的鞋里都是沙子。$s#$e#That's the trouble with living on the beach. / 这是在海边生活的小麻烦之一哦。",
        "event_idea1": "Mystery, huh? It's definitely an exciting genre. I'll remember that. / 很神奇吧？这种类型的确是很让人兴奋呢。真是终身难忘啊。",
        "Thu6": "Sometimes I wonder if I might just have an inflated self-image and no real skills...$s / 有时我觉得自己可能是太膨胀了，其实我并没有什么本事……$s#$e#No, no... I'm not fishing for compliments. Though they are appreciated... / 不，不……我这么说不是想让别人夸我。虽然我很希望得到表扬……",
        "fall_Tue": "It's been said that a pirate's ship, full of plundered gold, shipwrecked here a long time ago. / 据说在很久以前有一艘装满了黄金的海盗船在这里失事了。",
        "Introduction": "Ah, the new farmer we've all been expecting... and whose arrival has sparked many a conversation! / 啊，我们一直翘首以盼的新农民来啦……大家都在热议你哦！#$b#I'm Elliott... I live in the little cabin by the beach. It's a pleasure to meet you. / 我是艾利欧特……我住在海边的小屋里。很高兴认识你。",
        "summer_Sat": "The sun is angry today... My skin is a bit too delicate, I'm afraid. / 今天的太阳很毒啊……我怕我的皮肤太娇弱了。",
        "Sat6": "Some people are shy. Keep showing interest in them and they'll get comfortable around you. / 有些人比较羞涩。只要你时刻表现出对他们的兴趣，他们可能就会感觉在你身边非常舒服。#$e#Everyone likes to have friends, even that grumpy blacksmith. / 每个人都喜欢交朋友的，即使是那个脾气暴躁的铁匠也是啊。",
        "dating_Elliott": "I only wish I had given you a bouquet first!$l / 要是我先把花束给你就好了！$l",
        "Mon": "I'm kind of new to this town myself, but I really feel at home.$h / 我也刚到这个小镇不久，可是我已经在这里有了家的感觉。$h#$e#I moved here only a year before you. / 我只比你早一年搬到这里。",
        "Tue6": "The sweet friction of pen and paper is the music of my soul.$u / 纸与笔那美妙的摩擦声可是治愈我灵魂的音乐啊。$u#$b#That's why I chose this beach as my home, so that I could have peace and quiet to do my work. / 因此我以这片海滩为家，这样我就可以静静地完成我的工作了。",
        "AcceptGift_(O)814": "Ah, a bottle of fine ink. A writer can never have too much... and it's quite expensive! Thank you!$h / 这墨水可真是上乘，作家肯定要家中常备……这应该很贵吧！谢谢你！$h",
        "summer_Mon4": "I know that I am kind of an 'oddball'. / 我知道我有些“怪”。#$e#I hope you don't mind.$h / 希望你不要介意。$h",
        "FlowerDance_Decline": "Excuse me... not today.$s / 抱歉啊……今天不是时候。$s",
        "winter_Mon4": "@, you've trudged through the snow to visit me? / @，你冒着大雪来看我？#$e#I'm honored!$h / 我太荣幸了！$h",
        "Wed": "The forest is a wonderful place. Have you been there? / 森林可是个美妙的地方。你去过那里了吗？",
        "fall_Fri10": "@, when you're around... I feel unusually creative.$l / @，当你在我身边的时候，我感觉特别有创造力。$l#$e#I know... strange, but it's true. / 我知道……这种事奇怪，可这是真的。",
        "event_toast2": "That's a great idea!$h / 好主意！$h#$b#Here's to us! / 为我们干杯！",
        "fall_Sat": "It gets windy this time of year. Marvelous!$h / 每年的这个时候都会起风。太神奇了！$h",
        "AcceptBirthdayGift_Positive": "I'm honored that you would remember my birthday! Thank you!$h / 你还记得我的生日我很荣幸！谢谢你！$h",
        "Resort_Chair": "I'm just taking a quick break to slather some coconut oil on my body.$h / 我只是想稍作休息，往身上涂点椰子油。$h",
        "winter_Fri": "I have to brush my hair daily, or else it'll clump up into messy knots. / 我每天都要梳头，不然头发就会乱作一团。#$e#It's a lot of work. / 这可是很麻烦的。#$e#I'm surprised I haven't just shaved it off in a fit of passion.$h / 我居然没有一冲动就把它们都剃了？！$h#$e#I suppose I am too vain. / 我觉得可能是因为我太虚荣了吧。",
        "SquidFest": "It's rare to see so many people at the beach. All for the love of squid! / 看到这么多人到海滩来，有点稀奇。大家都很喜爱鱿鱼嘛！",
        "winter_Sun": "I really should scrub my floorboards today. I think an algae is starting to form.$s / 我今天还真该打扫一下地板了。好像都开始长苔藓了。$s#$e#Do you make time for cleaning? / 可以帮我打扫一下吗？",
        "GreenRain": "Let's not get in a tizzy, now... Gus! I propose a round of drinks to settle the nerves!%noturn / 可不要慌了神……格斯！为了镇定一下，我提议喝上一轮！%noturn",
        "fall_Mon": "Hello @. / 你好，@。#$e#Make sure and take breaks from your work now and then. / 要注意劳逸结合啊。",
        "breakUp": "Ah... the wilted bouquet. A sight I'd hoped to never see...$s / 啊……枯萎的花束。我真的不想看到这个……$s#$b#I suppose there are other horizons to set my eyes upon...$s / 也许我该去别的地方开阔一下视野……$s",
        "AcceptGift_(O)StardropTea": "Ah, what a gift! The aroma alone is inspiring... / 啊，这礼物真好！只是闻到香气我就很激动了……",
        "summer_Tue": "I've encountered some beautiful shells in front of my house. / 我在房子前面找到了许多漂亮的贝壳。#$e#I would imagine the rarer varieties to be quite valuable. / 可能是很有价值的稀有品种。",
        "winter_Tue10": "@, I had a feeling that you would show up. / @，我就知道你会来。#$e#Perhaps we're connected by an other-worldly thread.$l / 也许冥冥之中，有根线将我们联系在一起了呢。$l",
        "winter_Sat": "I've been doing little indoor exercises, since it's often too cold to go out. / 自从天气变得很冷后，我在室内也不怎么运动了。#$e#Sorry if it's a little humid in the cabin.$s / 如果这里很潮湿的话真是抱歉。$s",
        "AcceptGift_(O)154": "Agh, it's still wriggling! Get that abomination away from me!$6 [154] / 噫，怎么还在蠕动！快把这破玩意儿拿走！$6 [154]",
        "AcceptGift_Positive_forage_item_beach": "Ah, you've been doing some beach combing... A fine hobby! Thank you. / 啊，你是在赶海吧……这个爱好很不错啊！谢谢你。",
        "Sun6": "Oh, @! I was hoping you'd show up. / 哦……@！我正想着你什么时候来呢。#$e#It's always a pleasure to see you.$h / 见到你太高兴了。$h",
        "FlowerDance_Accept": "Of course... it would be an honor! I look forward to it.$h / 当然可以……我很荣幸！期待与你共舞。$h",
        "purchasedAnimal_Duck": "Did you know? A duck's feather makes for an excellent quill. / 你知道吗？鸭子的羽毛非常适合做羽毛笔。",
        "event_toast3": "Hmmph...forget it.$a / 嗯……别放在心上。$a",
        "AcceptGift_(O)444": "This will make a beautiful quill! I feel inspired already...$h / 这个做成羽毛笔肯定很漂亮！我已经开始文思泉涌了……$h",
        "Thu4": "I've been feeling hopeful lately. Perhaps the weather is changing. / 最近我觉得未来充满了希望。可能是因为季节变化了吧。",
        "Sat4": "Please excuse the sorry state of my cabin. / 请原谅我这里这么乱。",
        "summer_Sun": "You came all the way here just to talk to me? How kind.$h / 你大老远来就是为了和我聊聊天嘛？你真是个好人。$h",
        "eventSeen_39": "You've been very helpful... Now, I must think... / 谢谢你帮我忙……我得好好构思了……",
        "Thu8": "#$1 elliottApol#It's a little lonely out here on the beach... so I apologize if I was ever a little too forward with you when we first met. I was just eager to have a friend. / 在海滩上孤独地生活真是有点寂寞呢……我得道歉，在我们第一次见到的时候我有些太着急了。我只是太想交个朋友了。$k#$e#It feels good to have a close friend like you. / 有你这样的好朋友真好。",
        "fall_Sun": "I have to remember to water my plants today. And not with sea water this time! / 我得记住每天都要给作物浇水。当然，这回可不能用海水浇了！",
        "winter_Thu": "Breathe deeply. Do you notice it? That's the smell of the sea. / 深呼吸一下。你感受到了吗？大海的味道。#$e#How does it make you feel? / 你有什么感觉？",
        "event_idea2": "Ah, one of the classic genres. I'll remember that. / 啊，传统风格啊。真是终身难忘呢。",
        "Resort_Leaving_2": "Hopefully a crab hasn't snuck onto my clothes again.$s / 希望不要再有螃蟹偷偷钻进我的衣服里了。$s#$b#Imagine crawling out of a pocket and finding yourself on a beach hundreds of miles from home!$h / 想象一下你从口袋里爬出来，结果发现自己在离家数百公里的海滩上！$h#$e#Hmmm... Perhaps this could make for an interesting novel... / 嗯……也许这可以写成一本有趣的小说……",
        "fall_Tue8": "@, I was just thinking about you.$l / @，我刚刚还在想你的事情。$l#$e#Maybe you sensed it.$h / 你是不是感觉到啦？$h#$e#So! Tell me about your day. / 今天过得怎么样啊？",
        "Resort_2": "Oh dear! Some seaweed has tangled itself in my hair. / 啊，我的天！有海藻缠在我的头发上了。#$e#That's the trouble with relaxing on the beach. / 在海滩上度假就是会碰到这种麻烦。",
        "fall_Thu": "Oh dear! A tiny crab appears to have made his home in my shirt pocket.$l / 啊啊！一只小螃蟹好像把我的衬衫口袋当成家了。$l#$e#That's the trouble with living on the beach. / 这是在海边生活的小麻烦之一哦。",
        "GreenRain_2": "Ah, yet another unique day in the valley. Stimulating, to say the least! / 哎，星露谷又迎来独特的一天——何止是激动人心！",
        "AcceptGift_(O)155": "Agh, it's still wriggling! Get that abomination away from me!$6 [155] / 噫，怎么还在蠕动！快把这破玩意儿拿走！$6 [155]",
        "Resort": "I must admit, this beach blows my own humble strand out of the water. / 不得不承认，我那个小沙滩比起这个海滩根本不值一提。",
        "Thu2": "I can't seem to find the inspiration to begin writing my novel...$s / 我找不到小说开头的灵感啊……$s",
        "summer_Tue6": "I write in hopes of connecting with others through time and space.$u / 我之所以写作，是希望和他人建立时间与空间上的联系。$u#$e#*sigh*...times are changing, though. People don't read anymore.$s / *唉*……不过时代变了。人们再也不读书了。$s",
        "event_idea3": "I would've never guessed! I suppose even those of the 'earthiest' profession sometimes have their heads in the stars.$h / 真是想不到啊！就算是是那些“粗俗的”职业也有出人头地的一天。$h#$b#I'll remember that. / 我会铭记在心的。",
        "secondChance_Guys": "You've hurt me beyond measure... but I'm willing to leave the past behind us.$s / 你深深地伤害过我……但我愿意不计前嫌。$s",
        "summer_Mon6": "@, I know you have faith in my abilities as a writer. That means a lot to me.$h / @，我知道你对我的写作水平很有信心。这对我来说意义重大。$h",
        "Wed8": "Sorry, I'm feeling morose today.$s / 不好意思，今天我很郁闷。$s#$e#I wish there was more certainty about the future.$s / 真希望未来能更明确啊。$s#$e#I don't want to grow old as a lonely hermit on this beach...$s / 我可不想老了以后就在这里做个孤独的隐士啊……$s",
        "winter_Tue": "People have scraped a living off the sea for thousands of years. / 很多人可都是靠海为生，延续了上千年呢。#$e#I just go to the grocery store.$s / 我就是去趟杂货店。$s",
        "Sun": "Hello. I hope your new farming life is panning out as you'd hoped? / 你好。希望你在农场的新生活进展顺利啊。",
        "fall_Wed8": "I wouldn't mind trying my hand at farming. / 我试试做农活也不是不可以。#$e#The quiet atmosphere of a farm might be a good source of literary inspiration, don't you think?$h / 你不觉得农场那种安静的氛围很有助于发掘写作灵感吗？$h",
        "dating_Elliott_memory_oneday": "%Elliott whispers a sweet secret into your ear. / %艾利欧特在你耳边轻声说了一个甜甜的秘密。",
        "divorced": "...$s / ……$s#$e#Why do you torment me? Can't you see you've shattered all my hopes and dreams?$s / 为什么你要这么折磨我？你难道不知道你让我所有的希望和梦想都化为泡影了吗？$s",
        "wonIceFishing": "Well, if it isn't the town's number one ice fisher! That was truly an impressive performance.$h / 哎呀，这不是镇上数一数二的冰钓高手吗？你的表现真是太厉害了。$h#$e#I never stand a chance, but I always participate just to be sporting. / 我根本赢不过你，不过为了运动精神我还是会一直参加。",
        "event_boat2": "Oh! I'm so sorry.$8%fork / 噢！对不起。$8%fork",
        "winter_Thu6": "Breathe deeply. Do you notice it? That's the smell of the sea. / 深呼吸一下。你感受到了吗？大海的味道。#$e#Whenever I smell the sea, it reminds me of my youth. The ocean really impressed me as a child. / 每当闻到大海的味道，都会想起我小时候。小时候的大海真是给我留下了很深刻的印象。",
        "summer_Fri": "@? You look puzzled. / @？你看起来很迷惑的样子呢。#$b#I guess the hot summer air can make us a little dizzy. / 我看是夏天的热浪让我们头晕了。",
        "-winter_Wed": "A day can never be boring when you follow the whims of your imagination.$u / 只要有丰富的想象力你就不会感到无聊。$u#$e#Sorry, am I babbling on about nonsense? / 抱歉，我是不是太唠叨了？",
        "event_toast4": "Ah, to a harmonious future for the community... what a virtuous idea. / 啊，让社会有个更和谐美好的未来……多么高尚的想法啊。#$b#Here's to Pelican Town! / 为了鹈鹕镇干杯！",
        "Fri4": "Ah... do not get too close to my hair with a torch...$8 / 嘿……别拿着个火把离我头发这么近……$8",
        "Tue": "A great idea can pass through your head when you least expect it... but if your mind is too busy you might miss it. / 无心插柳柳成荫……如果你想得太多，反而会错过稍纵即逝的灵感。#$e#Well, I really must get back to my work. / 好吧，我真的得回去工作了。",
        "AcceptBirthdayGift_Negative": "Another year gone by, another gray hair... I suppose this gift can commemorate my decline.$s / 又过了一年，又一根白发……这个礼物也许可以作为我衰老的纪念。$s",
        "FlowerDance_Accept_Spouse": "Yes... could I refuse that soft, kind face? The touch of spring-time's sweet embrace? / 是的……我怎能拒绝那温柔、慈祥的面容？春天般的甜美拥抱？",
        "summer_Sun4": "Visit my cabin whenever you like. I could use the company.$h / 随时欢迎你来这里。能有人陪我说说话真是太好了。$h",
        "firstVisit_ElliottHouse": "Ah... please excuse the mess in my cabin. I wasn't expecting anyone to enter! / 啊……我屋子里很乱，不好意思，我没想到会有别人进来！",
        "Resort_Wander": "I've heard rumors of pirates coming to shore near here at night. They say it can get pretty wild! / 我听传闻说夜里会有海盗在附近上岸。听说会很刺激！",
        "summer_Wed": "It must be satisfying to follow your crop from seed to harvest. / 看着种子成长为成熟的作物一定感觉很心满意足吧。#$e#It's as if your essence is infused into the fruit.$u / 就好像你将自己的全部都注入到果实里了一样。$u",
        "Mon4": "I hope you've come to think of this place as 'home'. / 我希望你也能渐渐把这里当作“家”。",
        "fall_Mon4": "Come visit me if you need a break from your labors.$h / 要是干活累了就来我这里放松一下吧。$h#$e#I'm usually at my house. / 我经常都在家。",
        "AcceptGift_Positive_book_item": "Ah, a book... Yes, perhaps the prose within these pages will offer a new insight. Thank you. / 是书啊……真不错，这里面的文字或许能让我有新的灵感，谢谢你。",
        "summer_Mon": "A gentle little sunbeam woke me up this morning. I've never felt so refreshed.$u / 早上一抹温柔的阳光唤醒了我。我从未有过如此清爽的感觉。$u#$e#I'm sorry if that isn't very interesting to you. / 若你觉得无聊的话，我先说声抱歉了。",
        "event_boat1": "... I was worried you might not feel this way about another man.$l / ……我以前还担心你会对其他人会有不同的看法呢。$l^So am I.$l / 我也是。$l",
        "fall_Fri": "My legs are stiff from sitting at my writing desk all morning.$s / 在书桌前坐了一早上弄得我腿都麻了。$s",
        "fall_Fri4": "My legs are stiff from sitting at my writing desk all night.$s / 在书桌前坐了一整晚弄得我腿都麻了。$s#$e#Sometimes I envy you, @. / 有时我真羡慕你，@。",
        "married_Elliott": "You've plucked Pelican Town's finest flower... Now, you must care for it with all your heart. / 你摘下了鹈鹕镇最俊俏的一朵花……接下来你可要全心全意地呵护它。",
        "Sat": "You probably wouldn't like it inside my cabin. It's dark and full of spiders.$s / 你可能不会喜欢在我的小屋里待着。那里一片漆黑，还到处都是蜘蛛。$s",
        "eventSeen_40_memory_oneday": "I had a good time at the saloon the other day... Though my liver is not quite so enthusiastic... / 那天在酒吧玩得挺开心的……不过我的肝有点受不了……",
        "winter_Mon": "You've come to visit me in the cold? / 在这么冷的时候你还来看我？#$e#I could do with a respite from my lonely labors. / 我终于可以稍稍放下孤独的劳动、喘口气了。",
        "Fri": "The fresh air of this valley is good for body and mind. / 星露谷这里的空气对身体和心灵都很好哦。#$e#A quick stroll outdoors always invigorates me. / 在户外溜达溜达总是能让我振奋起来。",
        "Resort_Leaving": "I'll see you back in the valley. / 回头在谷里见。",
        "Resort_Bar": "Gus, I'll order a round for everyone! / 格斯，帮我给所有人点上一杯酒！#$b#*hic*... Oh... I don't have the G.$s / 嗝……哦……我没那么多钱。$s#$b#Heh heh... Never mind! / 哈哈哈……没关系！",
        "dumped_Guys": "Go away. I can't bear to see you.$s / 走开。我无法忍受再见到你。$s"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/Emily",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "AcceptGift_(O)68": "$c 0.5#Oh, wow... Thank you! This color perfectly captures my mood today.$h#The warm, soothing energy of this stone helps us re-center our thoughts... It's actually just what I needed on a day like this. Thanks! / $c 0.5#哇……谢谢你！这个颜色很符合我今天的心情。$h#这块宝石散发着温暖舒缓的能量，可以让人重新集中思绪……今天能收到这个真是太合适了，谢谢你！",
        "Mon6_inlaw_Haley": "I have to say, now that Haley's gone I've had a much easier time keeping things in order. / 不得不说，自从海莉走后，我的生活更井井有条了。",
        "Mon6": "I wish Haley would get a job or at least contribute to cooking and cleaning.$s / 我希望海莉可以找份工作，或者至少可以做做饭，打扫打扫房间。$s#$e#I think she's hoping to marry someone rich.$u / 我觉得她想嫁给有钱人。$u",
        "Resort_Entering": "Oh, I like this place! It's full of parrots! / 啊，这个地方真不错！好多鹦鹉！",
        "Thu": "I hope you're farming in a sustainable way. The valley's ecosystem is fragile! / 我希望你可以用可持续地的方法来耕作。星露谷的生态系统可是很脆弱的！#$e#How do I know? I have a strong gut-feeling! / 你问我怎么知道的？我的直觉可是很强的！",
        "summer_Thu": "I consider the bees and butterflies to be my special friends! / 我把蜜蜂和蝴蝶都当作是我的好朋友！",
        "reject_866": "Oh, that's beautiful... I have a friend who would love that! But she lives far from here... / 啊，真漂亮……我有个朋友，她一定会喜欢的！但她住得离这儿很远……",
        "fall_1": "Well, fall is here. Time to plant some new crops, huh? / 好啦，已经到秋天。该种些新的作物吧？",
        "fall_Tue": "Hello. Did you have a good summer? / 你好啊。这个夏天过得怎么样？",
        "Introduction": "Ooh!... I can read it on your face. You're going to love it here in Pelican Town. / 哦哦！……从你的表情我看得出来，你已经开始喜欢上鹈鹕镇这里了。#$b#If you're ever looking for something to do in the evening, stop by the saloon. That's where I work! / 你要是想过些夜生活的话，就去酒吧。我在那里工作哦！",
        "summer_Sat": "Don't overwork yourself or you might end up in Harvey's clinic! / 不要太勉强自己了，不然可能会被送进哈维的诊所哦！",
        "Sat6": "Do you ever think about the texture of fabric, @? Each texture has a distinct personality... feel my dress... see? / @，你有没有想过布料的材质？每种材质都有不同的个性……摸摸我的裙子……感觉到了吗？",
        "purchasedAnimal_Sheep": "Now that you have a sheep, you'll be able to make cloth! That'll open up a whole new world of tailoring possibilities. Just wait and see. / 有了绵羊之后，就能制作布料了！然后就可以打开缝纫世界的大门，拭目以待吧。",
        "fall_Mon8": "If I didn't have to work I'd suggest we go on a nice picnic! / 如果我没有工作的话我一定会提议去野餐的！",
        "Mon": "Have I told you Haley and I are sisters? Strange, isn't it? / 我和海莉是姐妹，这事我跟你说过吗？是不是很奇怪？",
        "Tue6": "Oh, hi... It's nice of you to visit me like this.$h / 噢，嗨……很高兴你来看我。$h",
        "secondChance_Girls": "@... I'm ready to give you a second chance. I still have faith that there's a good person inside of you.$s / @……我准备给你第二次机会。我仍然相信你的内在是个好人。$s",
        "summer_Mon4": "Eating healthy is very important to me. I want to live a long and active life. / 健康饮食是非常重要的。我希望能够长寿且始终保持精力充沛。",
        "FlowerDance_Decline": "I'm very sorry... but I've already agreed to dance with someone else.$u / 很抱歉……我已经答应与别人共舞了。$u",
        "fall_Wed": "My friend runs a shop in the desert. If you ever go there stop in and say hi for me. / 我的朋友在沙漠里开了个商店。如果你有机会去的话替我问个好。#$e#I think she sells some rare products. / 她好像是在卖一些稀有的商品。",
        "winter_Mon10": "Be careful an icicle doesn't fall on your head! I wouldn't want you to get hurt! / 小心别让冰柱砸到脑袋！我可不想让我最好的朋友受伤！",
        "Wed": "I've heard rumors of rare and powerful magic rings, forged long ago by forgotten civilizations. I'm not sure if it's true or just a fairy tale. / 我听说过一些关于稀世魔戒的传言。据说这些戒指由失落的文明所打造。我也不知道是不是真的。",
        "dumped_Girls": "...$s / ……$s",
        "event_dance2": "Um... Okay. Sorry you didn't like it. I guess those three years of practice were a complete waste...$s / 呃……好吧。真是抱歉，原来你不喜欢啊。我觉得那三个月的练习真是浪费时间啊……$s",
        "fall_Sat": "Keep your mind open and some interesting things might take root. / 想开一点，有趣的事情可能就会发生哦。#$e#Anyway, how is your day going? / 对了，今天过得怎么样？",
        "AcceptBirthdayGift_Positive": "Oh, you remembered my birthday! Thanks, @! That's really nice of you.$h / 啊，你还记得我的生日！@，谢谢你！你有心了。$h",
        "AcceptGift_(O)62": "$c 0.5#It's so smooth! When I hold it... I can feel the energy of all the mermaids in the sea. Thank you!#Thank you! I'm gonna put this under my pillow, and hopefully I'll dream about the ocean. / $c 0.5#好光滑啊！拿着的时候……我能感受到来自大海里美人鱼的力量。谢谢你！#谢谢你！我要放在枕头下面，晚上说不定能梦到大海呢。",
        "Resort_Chair": "Are you having fun, @? You need to remember to take breaks now and then too! / @，你玩得开心吗？累了的话，记得休息一下！",
        "fall_Thu8": "I think Clint's mad at me. He never looks at me anymore...$u / 克林特好像在生我的气。他也再不来看我了……$u#$e#I always thought we were friends.$u / 我还一直以为我们是朋友。$u",
        "winter_Fri": "If I wasn't so busy I'd help you dig around in that cave by the lake. / 如果我不这么忙的话，我挺想帮你在湖边的那个洞里翻一翻的。#$e#I bet there are some powerful crystals inside there. / 我觉得在那里肯定有鱼在冬眠。",
        "summer_Fri6": "You know, I'm sure Gus would understand if I wanted to leave the Saloon someday. / 如果有一天我想离开酒吧，我相信格斯会理解的。#$b#There's so much out there, I can't stay a barmaid forever.$u / 有这么多机会，我不能永远做一个酒吧女招待。$u",
        "Tue8": "You know, @... I think the future looks bright for both of us. / @……我认为我们的未来都很光明。",
        "event_dance1": "Thank you! / 非常感谢！",
        "winter_Sun": "Hi! / 嗨！#$e#...Yes? / ……有事吗？",
        "dating_Emily_memory_oneday": "We're going to have a lot of fun together, I just know it.$h / 我们在一起会很开心的，肯定会。$h",
        "GreenRain": "There must be a meaning behind this... Nature is trying to tell us something.$3 / 这背后肯定有什么深意……大自然在向我们传递信号。$3#$e#What, though? I can't tell... It's hard to read. I feel a strong presence, though...$3 / 具体是什么呢？我分辨不出来……实在太难懂了。不过，我感受到一个强大的存在……$3",
        "fall_Mon": "It's good weather for a picnic, isn't it? / 这是个野餐的好季节，对不对？",
        "breakUp": "B...But I thought we had a special bond... *sniff*$s / 但……但是我以为我们之前有特殊的牵绊……（抽鼻子）$s",
        "AcceptGift_(O)StardropTea": "Wow, thank you! I've heard that if you drink this before bed you'll have vivid dreams. / 哇，谢谢你！我听说如果你睡前喝这个，晚上做梦会感觉身临其境。",
        "AcceptGift_(O)64": "$c 0.5#Wow, look at that color! It matches perfectly with my outfit.$h#Oh, this is perfect... I've been feeling a little sluggish lately. Rubies are great for energizing the spirit! / $c 0.5#哇，这个颜色！跟我的衣服很搭。$h#哎，这可太好了……最近我有点怠惰，有了红宝石肯定能振奋起来！",
        "dating_Emily": "%Emily has a big smile on her face. / %艾米丽笑得很开心。",
        "eventSeen_4081148": "Hey, I saw you at Sam's show. It was fun!$h / 哎，你也去看山姆的演出了吧，真好看！$h#$e#The city smelled pretty bad, though.$s / 就是城里感觉好脏。$s",
        "Tue4": "I'm just working at Gus' to make ends meet... but my real passion is tailoring.$u / 我在格斯酒吧工作只是为了维生……可是我真正的梦想是当裁缝。$u#$e#I made these clothes from scratch, see? / 你看，这些衣服都是我亲手缝的哦。",
        "summer_Tue": "Hello there, @. / 你好啊，@。#$e#I feel lazy today.$u / 我今天感觉一动都不想动。$u",
        "AcceptGift_(O)60": "$c 0.5#Oh!... Heheh... I know exactly why you gave me this stone today. Very interesting...#Wow, it's beautiful! This color makes me think of all the spiritual power within the forest... Can you feel that wood energy? / $c 0.5#啊！……嘿嘿……我知道你今天为什么送我这块宝石了，真有意思……#哇，好漂亮！这个颜色让我想到了森林中的灵力……你能感受到里面蕴藏着树木的力量吗？",
        "winter_Sat": "Do you know how to cook 'Bean Hotpot'? / 你会做“豆类火锅”吗？#$e#I like that dish quite a bit.$h%revealtaste:Emily:207 / 我很喜欢那道菜。$h%revealtaste:Emily:207#$e#It's hard to get fresh ingredients in the winter, huh? / 不过在冬天想要获得新鲜的食材很难啊，是不是？",
        "eventSeen_471942": "Hello @. I had a feeling I'd be seeing you today. / @，你好，我有预感今天会碰到你。",
        "fall_Sat6": "I don't have any huge plans for life. I prefer not to stress about the future. / 我没什么远大的计划。我也不想因思考未来变得紧张兮兮的。",
        "FlowerDance_Accept": "Yes, I'd love to dance with you, @!$h / 好啊，我可以跟你跳舞！$h#$e#Now I'm excited... This is going to be a lot of fun! / 我有点兴奋……感觉会很开心！",
        "Resort_Shore": "Can you feel it? The ocean has a profound healing energy. / 你能感觉到吗？海洋有着深厚的治愈能量。",
        "AcceptGift_(TR)ParrotEgg": "Oh, good, it's still warm... Poor thing, where's it's mother? *Whisper* ...I'll be your mother, don't worry... Poor baby.$s / 啊，幸好还有点温度……可怜的小家伙，它的妈妈怎么了？（柔声说）……别担心，妈妈在这里……太可怜了。$s#$b#I'm glad you gave this to me, @. I'll take very good care of it. / @，你送我这个我很开心，我会好好照顾它的。",
        "Mon2": "I have a secret hobby, but I won't say any more. / 我有一个不为人知的爱好，但我不会说。#$e#Maybe I'll show you some day.$h / 也许有一天我会告诉你。$h",
        "eventSeen_101_memory_oneweek": "My outing with Clint was pretty fun! / 之前和克林特出去玩挺开心的！#$b#Although, he spilled a root beer all over himself within ten minutes of getting there, and then barely said a word the rest of the night.$3 / 不过他刚到那里十分钟就把根汁汽水洒了一身，然后一整晚都很沉默。$3",
        "Thu4": "Sometimes the flowers speak to me... each one has a different story to tell! / 有时候，花儿会跟我说话……每一朵都在诉说着不同的故事！",
        "AcceptGift_(O)70": "$c 0.5#That's funny, I had a dream that you would give me a piece of jade today!$h#Ooh, it's jade! This is supposed to attract wealth... And who couldn't do with a few extra coins in the pocket?$h / $c 0.5#我昨晚梦见你会送我一块翡翠，真有意思！$h#哎，这是翡翠吧！据说翡翠能招财……谁会跟钱过不去呢？$h",
        "summer_Sun": "Hi @! / 嗨，@！",
        "Wed6": "Have faith... every day you're taking one more step on the path of your destiny. / 心怀信念……每一天，你都向目标迈进了一步。",
        "fall_Sun": "Nothing like a sunny Sunday to lift the spirits! / 阳光明媚的日子果然能让人振作啊！",
        "eventSeen_11_memory_oneweek": "Have you ever tried cooking without a recipe? It's kind of liberating. / 你试过不按照食谱做菜吗？会感觉很自由。#$b#And who knows... you might discover something amazing! / 而且……说不准会发现不得了的东西！",
        "winter_Thu": "It must be so cold for the poor fish.$s / 这些可怜的鱼一定感觉很冷吧。$s#$e#I wonder if any fish hibernate? Maybe I should ask Demetrius. / 不知道鱼会不会冬眠啊？也许我可以去问问德米特里厄斯。",
        "summer_Mon_inlaw_Haley": "Haley and I get along much better now that she's moved out. I look forward to her visits! / 海莉搬走之后，我俩的关系就好多了。我现在很盼望她能来看看我！",
        "fall_Tue4": "Hi @! I bet your farm did great this past summer, huh? / 嗨，@！这个夏天，你的农场经营得不错吧？#$e#You're an excellent farmer.$h / 你真是个出色的农夫。$h",
        "fall_Thu": "Are you friends with Clint? He's a nice guy, if you get to know him. / 你们是克林特的朋友吗？认识他以后你就会发现，他是个好人。#$e#He gets lonely working in his shop all day. But he's so shy he has trouble making new friends. / 他整天都闷在商店里工作，所以感觉很孤独。不过他很害羞，导致他交朋友有些困难。",
        "GreenRain_2": "Can you feel it? The forest is singing! The trees are dancing with joy! / 你感受到了吗？森林在歌唱！大树在欢快地跳舞！",
        "winter_Wed": "Haley and I aren't made for such a big house. It's a hassle to keep it clean. / 海莉和我生来就没有住大房子的命。打扫大房子真是太难了。#$e#Ah well. I really shouldn't be complaining. / 啊，我不该这么抱怨。#$e#Your farmhouse seems nice and cozy.$h / 你的农舍看起来真是温馨又舒适啊。$h",
        "Resort": "If you open your heart to the sun, you can feel a loving energy inside of you.$h / 如果你向太阳敞开心扉，就能在体内感受到爱的能量。$h",
        "summer_Tue6": "I feel bad for Linus. People judge him, but he's just living a different lifestyle.$u / 莱纳斯真是可怜。人们总对他怀有偏见，但他只是生活方式和别人不一样而已。$u#$e#I wish everyone could learn to be accepting of others. / 我希望大家都能学会接受别人。",
        "married_Haley": "That was a beautiful wedding... I'm really happy for you and Haley!$h / 你们的婚礼好浪漫……你跟海莉在一起，真是太好了！$h",
        "Wed8": "$query PLAYER_NPC_RELATIONSHIP current any married roommate#Hey, @. / $query PLAYER_NPC_RELATIONSHIP current any married roommate#哎，@。#$e#I always knew we would become good friends. It was written in the stars!|Hi, @.$u / 我就知道我们会成为好朋友。这是命中注定的！|@，你好啊。$u#$e#I always knew we'd become close like this... / 我就知道我们会成为亲密无间的朋友……",
        "winter_Tue": "Oh, hello @!$h / 哦，你好啊，@！$h#$e#You must be getting very good at farming by now, huh? / 你现在是不是很擅长种地了？",
        "winter_Tue4": "I think my hair is frozen solid...$s / 我感觉我的头发冻得硬邦邦的……！$s",
        "Sun": "Hi @! / 嗨，@！#$e#Do you raise sheep in your barn? You can turn their wool into beautiful bolts of cloth! / 你养没养绵羊啊？它们的毛可以织成非常漂亮的布料！#$e#You'll need a loom, though. You can make them yourself if you know the crafting recipe. / 不过，你需要一台织布机。如果你知道怎么做的话可以自己做一个。",
        "winter_Sun6": "My sister and I might fight sometimes, but I would really miss her if she left. / 我和我的妹妹有时会打架。不过她要是真离开了，我会非常想她的。#$e#I think she'll become a very nice young lady some day... Don't tell her I said that.$h / 我觉得她有一天会成为一名善良的女性……别让她知道是我说的哦。$h#$e#So, is there anything you want to talk about? / 所以说，你想聊些什么吗？",
        "divorced": "@... You broke my heart... I just can't talk to you anymore.$s / @……你让我心都碎了……我不能再和你说话了。$s#$e#Please, let me try to heal...$s / 求求你，我要平静一下……$s",
        "fall_15": "$d bus#I'm visiting Sandy today. We're best friends! / 我今天要去找桑迪玩，我们超级要好的！#$e#I'm really happy that the bus is repaired. / 幸好巴士已经修好了。|*Sigh*... If only that old bus were fixed, I would've visited my friend Sandy today... / 唉……假如那辆破巴士修好了，我今天肯定就去找我的朋友桑迪玩了……$s",
        "eventSeen_2123343_memory_oneday": "I won't forget our camping trip any time soon...$l / 那天的露营我会一直记得的……$l",
        "Sun4": "This house was left in our care by my parents. They've been traveling the world for the last two years. / 父母把房子交给我们照看。他们在过去两年里都在环游世界。#$e#We have no idea when they'll be back. / 我们不知道他们什么时候会回来。#$e#I enjoy living here, though. It's a beautiful area and the town is nice. / 不过我很喜欢在这里生活。这里很漂亮，小镇也很棒。",
        "Mon8": "There's good people in this town who just can't seem to find happiness. It makes me sad.$u / 这个小镇有些人虽然很善良，但还是找不到属于自己的幸福。这让我伤心。$u#$e#Working in the saloon, I hear first-hand about everyone's problems.$u / 由于我在酒吧工作，所以也能听到各种酸甜苦辣，人间冷暖。$u",
        "eventSeen_463391": "Nothing is more sad than an injured animal...$s / 小动物受伤实在太糟心了……$s",
        "summer_Fri": "If I wasn't so busy I'd come help you on the farm! / 如果不忙的话我会去农场帮你的！#$e#But Gus would be upset if I had another job...$s / 不过如果我有别的工作了格斯会不高兴了……$s",
        "summer_Sun6": "Hi, @! We've become decent friends, haven't we?$h / 嗨，@！我们已经是好朋友了，对不对？$h#$e#That's fine with me. You're a cool guy. / 我觉得很好。你人很好。^I'm glad.$h / 我很高兴。$h",
        "divorced_Haley": "Haley is too proud to be heartbroken over the divorce... Or at least to show it.$3 / 海莉自尊心太强，离婚了也没有很伤心……至少她没表现出来。$3",
        "Tue": "I work part-time at Gus' saloon. It pays the bills. / 我在格斯酒吧兼职。赚的钱能解决好大问题呢。",
        "AcceptBirthdayGift_Negative": "Oh, you remembered my birthday! Thanks, @! That's really ni--$h / 啊，你还记得我的生日！@，谢谢你！你——$h#$b#...*sniff*...*sniff*... what is that smell?$s / ……（闻了两下）……什么味道？$s#$b#... What is this...?$s / ……这是什么东西……？$s",
        "fall_Sun10": "You're such a nice person, @! Thanks for being my friend.$h / 你真是个好人，@！谢谢你成为我的朋友。$h",
        "winter_Sun6_inlaw_Haley": "Say hi to my sister for me! And remind her to visit me tomorrow. / 代我向我妹妹问好！还有，提醒她明天来看我。",
        "FlowerDance_Accept_Spouse": "Of course, my love. I've been looking forward to this!$h / 当然好呀，甜心。我期待这一刻很久了！$h",
        "summer_Sun4": "It's around this time of year that my good friends visit the region... I mean the parrots! / 每年一到这个时候，我的好朋友就会过来……我说的是鹦鹉哦！",
        "summer_Wed": "It doesn't rain much in summer, does it? / 夏天不怎么下雨对吧？#$e#That just means more watering work for you, huh? / 对你来说可意味着要浇更多的水了，是不是？#$e#Or do you enjoy the sunny weather? / 还是说你喜欢烈日炎炎的夏天呢？",
        "Resort_Dance": "%Emily is lost in the music. / %艾米丽沉醉在音乐里。",
        "Mon4": "This world is full of spirits and magic... Some don't believe me, but I know it's true. / 这个世界充斥着幽灵与魔法……有些人不相信我，但我知道这是真的。#$e#I can see it in your eyes... you believe in the other world, like me. / 我从你眼睛里可以看出来……你相信异世界的存在，就像我一样。",
        "married_Shane": "Well, now that you're married, I assume Shane won't be coming to the Saloon as much! / 唔，既然谢恩跟你结婚了，他之后就不太会来酒吧了吧！#$e#That's probably a good thing, but it's always a little sad to lose a regular...$s / 其实挺好的，不过少了些人气还是有点遗憾……$s",
        "summer_Mon": "Haley is a picky eater. It's so hard to cook for her. / 海莉的嘴巴可挑剔了。给她做饭很难啊。",
        "Wed4": "You catch fish? I just hope you treat the poor things humanely.$s / 你还捕鱼啊？我只是希望你能善待那些可怜的小家伙。$s#$e#Every critter deserves our respect, even the slimy ones. / 就算是这些黏不溜秋的生物，我们也要心怀敬意。",
        "fall_Fri": "Another beautiful fall day. / 又是个秋高气爽的好日子。#$e#It's a pity it'll soon be over. / 想想这样的日子马上就要结束了还真是遗憾啊。",
        "AcceptGift_(O)66": "$c 0.5#Oh, it's beautiful, @! I hope you didn't put yourself in too much danger to get this.$h#Ah, an amethyst! This will protect me on those late nights working at the Saloon. / $c 0.5#哇，@，这个好漂亮！但愿你找它的时候没有冒着太大的危险。$h#哎，这是紫水晶吧！希望我去酒吧工作到深夜的时候，它能保护我。",
        "event_dance3": "Did you really think so? That's exactly the effect I was shooting for!$h / 你真这么想吗？那正是我想达到的效果！$h#$b#I'm so glad you liked it. / 我很高兴你能喜欢。",
        "Sat": "I like making my own clothes, but it's not easy to get cloth. / 我喜欢自己做衣服，可是要弄到布料不是很容易。#$e#And it's such a long trip to the city. / 要走好远才能走到城市啊。",
        "fall_Sun6": "There's so many invisible barriers holding us back. Why can't people learn to let go and explore their true potential? / 有很多无形的壁垒阻碍了我们前进的步伐。为什么人们不能学会放下包袱、迎接自由呢？#$e#Me? Well, you know what they say... 'You can't cage a wild Junimo'. / 我吗？你知道他们是怎么说的吗………“你无法将野生的祝尼魔关进笼子里”。",
        "winter_Mon": "Be careful an icicle doesn't fall on your head! / 小心别让冰柱砸到脑袋！",
        "Fri": "Ah, spring. The season of pastels. I actually prefer jewel tones, myself. / 春天啊，缤纷的季节。个人来讲我很喜欢宝石色调的。#$b#Oh, excuse me! I was mumbling about fashion again, wasn't I? / 哦，抱歉！我是不是又开始嘀咕关于流行的东西了？",
        "Resort_Leaving": "Ah... my lungs feel perfect. / 啊……呼吸好舒畅。",
        "winter_Tue2": "I bet you're an excellent farmer by now! / 我敢打赌，你现在一定已经成为了一个优秀的农场主！",
        "Resort_Bar": "It's nice to be on this side of the bar for once!$h / 能在酒吧当一次顾客真是奇妙！$h",
        "fall_Fri6": "Smell that clean air? It's lovely, isn't it? / 呼吸到这清新的空气了吗？是不是很棒？#$b#I just fear that the Joja Co.'s of the world will take this away from us.$u / 我就害怕 Joja 公司会毁掉这新鲜的空气。$u",
        "summer_Sun8": "Hi, @! We've become decent friends, haven't we?$h / @你好！我们已经是好朋友了吧？$h#$e#This may sound weird, but I've always been certain this would happen. / 虽然感觉有点怪怪的，但我一直相信我们能成为好朋友。"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/Evelyn",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "fall_Thu": "Today I'm baking cookies. They're shaped like little pumpkins.$h / 我今天要烤些饼干。是小南瓜形状的哦。$h#$e#Maybe I'll tell you my recipe one of these days. / 以后我没准会把做法告诉你哦。",
        "GreenRain_2": "The flowers seem to love this rain... / 这场雨下来，花应该会长得更好……",
        "winter_Wed": "I usually tend to the gardens, but they're covered in snow. / 我经常去花园，但是它们现在被雪盖住了。#$e#I still like to check up on them now and then. / 如今我仍然喜欢时不时去看看。",
        "Thu": "I'll be baking cookies today. I like to make flower shapes in the spring.$h / 今天我要烤点曲奇。春天的时候，我喜欢把曲奇做成花瓣形状的。$h#$e#Maybe I'll tell you my recipe one of these days. / 以后我没准会把做法告诉你哦。",
        "summer_Thu": "I'm going to bake cookies today. They're coconut wonders shaped like little palm trees! Heehee.$h / 我今天要烤些饼干。好吃的椰子味哦，连形状也是椰树形的！嘻嘻。$h#$e#Maybe I'll tell you my recipe one of these days. / 以后我没准会把做法告诉你哦。",
        "winter_Sat8": "@, have I told you that George and I have lived in our house for 30 years? / @，我跟你说过我和乔治在我们的房子里已经住了 30 年了吗？#$e#I hope you stay here for a while.$h / 我希望你再多留一阵子。$h",
        "reject_866": "That's a very pretty rose, dear. Have you shown it to Emily? It makes me think of her. / 亲爱的，这朵玫瑰花真漂亮。你给艾米丽看过了吗？这让我想起了她。",
        "fall_Tue": "I've been putting raisins in George's oatmeal... but he hasn't said a word. I wonder if he even notices these things? / 我在乔治的燕麦里面放了葡萄干……但他一句话都没说。我在想他到底注意到没有？",
        "Introduction": "Why, hello and welcome to our little community, dear!  / 啊，欢迎你来我们的小家园啊，亲爱的！#$b#You can call me 'Granny' if you like.$h / 如果乐意的话，就叫我“奶奶”吧。$h",
        "cropMatured_591": "Home-grown tulips make for a lovely springtime gift. / 春天送别人一枝自家种的郁金香，那是极好的。",
        "summer_Sat": "Be careful out there, dear. You could get sunburnt! / 在外面注意点。你可能会被晒伤的！",
        "Mon": "Oh my! What a lovely day.$u / 哎呀！天气真好啊。$u",
        "Tue6": "It's nice of you to take the time to visit George and I. / 谢谢你来看我和乔治。#$e#Without young people around, we'd age much faster.$h / 没有年轻人陪着我们的话，我们可能就老得更快了。$h",
        "summer_Thu4": "It seems like we always have more visitors when I start baking cookies. / 好像我一烤饼干就总有很多客人来。#$e#My mother taught me the recipe. / 配方是我妈妈教我的。",
        "winter_Tue": "Aren't you cold? You should wear a thicker jacket, my dear! / 你不冷吗？亲爱的，你应该穿件更厚的外套。#$e#This weather isn't good for my joints...$s / 这天气对我的关节不好……$s",
        "MovieInvitation": "Oh my! That's so kind of you, dear. Why yes... I'd love to go to the movies!$h / 哎呀！你真好，亲爱的。当然了……我很愿意去看电影！$h#$b#You go on ahead, and I'll meet you at the theater. / 你先去吧，我们电影院见。",
        "GreenRainFinished": "Oh, my dear... I'm so glad everything ended up okay. And my flowers look healthier than ever! / 我的天哪……大家没事真的太好了。我的花好像还长得更好了！",
        "fall_Sat_inlaw_Alex": "Oh, hello my dear. I think of you as my own ${grandson^grand-daughter}$ now.$h / 哦，你好啊，亲爱的。我现在把你当做我的亲孙${子^女}$。$h",
        "fall_Wed": "The good Mayor put me in charge of the town's public gardens. / 镇长人不错，他让我负责全镇的公共花园。#$e#The fall flowers are delicate, so don't go stomping on them! I know how you kids like to do. / 秋天的花很娇贵，所以别进去踩！我知道你们这些孩子就喜欢这样干。",
        "AcceptGift_(O)170": "Thank you, dear. I've been looking everywhere for my reading glasses... / 亲爱的，谢谢你，我找了半天都没找到我的老花镜……#$b#My, my! They've become filthy... / 哎呦喂！怎么弄这么脏……",
        "Sun": "It's nice to be so close to the ocean. The sound of the sea makes going to sleep a lot easier. / 离大海这么近真好。海的声音让我安然入睡。#$e#As kids we hunted for seashells after the tide went out. Those were the days... / 小时候我们总在退潮后去找贝壳。那些日子真是……",
        "Wed": "#$1 evelynGarden1#I saw the most beautiful family of butterflies sunning themselves in the town garden yesterday. / 我昨天在花园里看见了一群蝴蝶，真是美丽至极。$k#$e#The good Mayor put me in charge of the town's public gardens. / 镇长人不错，他让我负责全镇的公共花园。#$e#I've been working on the town flower beds for weeks, so don't step on them! / 这个园圃，我已经护理数周了，可不要随意踩踏啊！",
        "fall_Sat": "Are you friends with Alex? / 你们是亚历克斯的朋友吗？#$e#Sometime he worries me sick. / 他有时候总担心我生病。",
        "pamHouseUpgrade": "Oh, sweetie... that was so nice of you to put Pam up in a beautiful new house!$h / 哦，甜心……你真好，让潘姆住进一间美丽的新房子！$h#$e#It warms my heart when people take care of each other like that... / 当人们像这样照顾彼此时，我的心暖暖的……",
        "cc_Complete": "It's lovely to have the old community center back. We have so many memories from the old days... It's a special place. / 社区中心能恢复真是太好了，以前可喜欢待在那里了……对我们来说意义非凡。",
        "married": "I'm very happy for you, dear.$h / 亲爱的，我真为你高兴。$h#$e#Seeing young people in love is heartwarming for old grannies like me. / 看到年轻人相爱，我这个老婆婆心里暖洋洋的。",
        "divorce": "Next time you marry, make sure it's the right one...$s / 下次结婚的时候，你一定要找到真爱啊……$s",
        "winter_Sun": "You should make some hot soup to stay warm. / 你应该煲点热汤暖暖身子。#$e#And make sure you wear a jacket! / 别忘了穿上夹克！",
        "GreenRain": "George, dear... Is this the end? It's been a good life, but I'd like to see Alex find his way before departing...$s%noturn / 乔治，老头子……末日来了吗？我一生过得挺好的，假如能看到亚历克斯出息的那一天，我就死而无憾了……$s%noturn",
        "fall_Mon": "With every year I appreciate the seasons more and more. For young people it's easy to let them slip by. / 随着时间流逝，我越来越喜欢各个季节。对于年轻人来说，总是让这些美好的时光悄悄流逝呢。",
        "Tue": "Don't mind my husband, George. He isn't very friendly to strangers. / 不要在意我的丈夫，乔治。他对陌生人不太友好。#$e#If you get to know him better he'll warm up to you. / 要是你和他熟了以后他会对你很热情的。#$e#I'm sure you two could become good friends one day!$h / 我相信你们有一天会成为好朋友的！$h#$e#Since you're so interested in my husband I'll let you in on a little secret: he really likes leeks! You can find them in the mountains this time of year. / 既然你对他很感兴趣，我可以告诉你一个小秘密：他很喜欢韭菜！在这个时节，你可以到山里摘一些给他。",
        "AcceptGift_(O)StardropTea": "Oh, you're giving this to me? Thank you so much, dear. This is a really special gift! / 啊，这个是送给我的吗？亲爱的，谢谢你啊，这个礼物很特别！",
        "winter_Sat6": "Oh... my dear. You have your grandfather's eyes...$s / 哦……亲爱的！你的眼睛跟你爷爷的一样……$s#$e#Yes... yes... I knew him very well. / 对……对……我跟他很熟。",
        "summer_Mon_inlaw_Alex": "How's my grandson doing? I imagine he's quite happy living on the farm. / 我的孙子怎么样了？我想他住在农场里应该很开心。#$e#He deserves to be happy... he's a good boy. / 他应该得到幸福……他是个好孩子。",
        "Event_cookies2": "What was that, dear? I could've sworn you said 'hockey puck'. *sigh* My ears aren't what they used to be.$s / 亲爱的，你说什么？我听到你说的是“冰球”。*唉* 我的耳朵不像以前那么好使了。$s",
        "summer_Tue": "George is always a little less grumpy in the summer. The warm weather softens his bones. / 乔治夏天的时候脾气没那么暴躁……温暖的天气让他的骨头发软。#$e#You might not be able to tell, but I can. I've known him for sixty years! / 你可能看不出来，但是我能。我认识他六十年了！",
        "winter_Sat": "We've lived here for over 30 years. / 我们在这里已经住了 30 多年了。#$e#We've seen a lot of people come and go. Your grandfather, for one. Bless him... *sigh* / 我们见惯了人来人往。比如你的爷爷。上帝保佑……*唉*",
        "summer_Wed": "The good Mayor put me in charge of the town's public gardens. / 镇长人不错，他让我负责全镇的公共花园。#$e#I've been working on the town flower beds for months, so don't step on them! / 这个园圃我已经护理数周了，可不要随意踩踏啊！",
        "AcceptGift_Positive_forage_item_beach": "Thank you, dear. This brings back such sweet memories... / 亲爱的，谢谢你。这让我想起了美好的时光……",
        "reject_867": "Oh, I'm sure George would be interested in that! / 啊，乔治肯定会很感兴趣！",
        "summer_Mon": "I feel more energetic in this wonderful weather.$u / 在这种好天气里我感觉更有活力了。$u",
        "summer_Sun": "Sweet peas are in bloom right now. / 甜豌豆花正开着呢。#$e#They've got such a wonderful fragrance, haven't they? / 真好闻啊，不是吗？",
        "pamHouseUpgradeAnonymous": "Call me a silly old fool... but I think I have an idea who paid for Pam's new house... *wink* / 虽然你可以叫我蠢蠢的老傻瓜……但我想我知道，谁为潘姆买了新房子……*眨眼*",
        "Event_cookies1": "Thank you!$h / 非常感谢！$h",
        "Sat": "I used to love looking at the clouds, but I have trouble seeing them these days. / 我喜欢看云彩，不过现在是看不到了。#$e# My eyes just don't work as well as they used to.$s / 我的眼睛不像以前那么好使了。$s",
        "fall_Sun": "My eyesight may be poor, but my nose hasn't failed me yet! / 我视力可能不太好，但是鼻子很灵！#$e#I can smell fallen leaves and mushrooms. It reminds me of the forests I used to play in as a girl. / 我能闻到落叶和蘑菇的味道。这使我想起了我还是小女孩的时候去玩耍的森林。",
        "winter_Mon": "Be careful you don't slip on the ice, dear. / 小心别在冰上滑倒了哦。",
        "winter_Thu": "Today I'm baking cookies. They're shaped like little winter stars.$h / 今天我要烤饼干，形状像是小小的冬日之星。$h#$e#Maybe I'll tell you my recipe one of these days. / 之后有机会我可以把做法告诉你。",
        "Fri": "George spends the whole day in front of that darned television set. / 乔治一整天都坐在那该死的电视前。#$e#I wish he'd go outside more. Some fresh air would do him good. / 我希望他能多出去走走。呼吸点新鲜空气对他有好处。"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/George",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "GreenRain_2": "Looks like the young folks will have to do some extra weeding after this one...Heheh...$h / 这场雨下完就要除草，年轻人有得好忙了……嘿嘿……$h",
        "Mon6": "I'm surprised you want to be friends with an old-timer like me. / 我很惊讶你愿意和像我一样的老前辈做朋友。",
        "divorced_once": "Hmmph... took the easy way out, huh? / 哼……遇到困难就退缩了是吧？#$e#People these days treat marriage like a television set... If you get bored, just change the channel! Back in my day... *grumble* / 这年头，结婚就跟看电视一样……要是厌倦了，换个频道就完事了！我年轻的时候啊……（发牢骚）",
        "GreenRain": "There, there, honey... Don't you worry.%noturn / 亲爱的，没事的，没事的……别操心了。%noturn#$b#Even if it is poisonous, I breathed in more noxious gas in one minute back in the ol' coal mines... And I'm still kickin'! / 即使有毒，我当初在煤矿里待一分钟，吸到的毒气都比这多……我不还是活得好好的！",
        "Fri8": "I've been thinking...Maybe I've been a little bit of a grouch.$s / 我一直在想……是不是我有点太爱发牢骚了。$s#$e#I used to think no one cared about us old folks. / 我以为没人会在乎我们这些老家伙。",
        "WinterStar_GiveGift_After": "You don't like it, huh? Bah! Kids these days... no appreciation for anything. That was expensive, and I'm not made of money, you know! / 你不喜欢是吧？呵！现在的年轻人……什么都不懂得珍惜。我又不是什么有钱人，买这个可贵了！",
        "Thu": "I can't talk right now, young man. / 我现在没空聊天，小伙子。^I can't talk right now, miss. / 我现在没空聊天，小姐。#$e#My favorite program is on. / 我最喜欢的节目正演着呢。",
        "Tue": "Hmmph... Looks like another gloomy day.$s / 嗯……貌似又是阴沉的一天。$s",
        "AcceptGift_(O)StardropTea": "Hmm... *sip*... ahhh... Tastes just like Mama's tuna casserole! Delicious! / 唔……（喝了一口）……啊……这是我妈妈做的金枪鱼砂锅的味道！好喝！",
        "accept_867": "What's this? / 这是什么？#$b#Hmmph... so you push this button first? What's this button do? Hmmph... *grumble* / 唔……所以你是先按了这个按键？这个按键是用来做什么的？嗯……（咕哝）#$b#Hehe! Well, how about that! It's a new channel!$h / 哈哈！嗯，看看这个！是新的频道！$h#$b#Here, take this. It's a stone I found when I was a coal miner back in the day. Funny thing, it's glowed blue and stayed cold for over forty years. Like magic! / 给，拿着这个。这是我当年挖矿的时候发现的一块石头。四十年来，它一直冰凉冰凉的，还发着蓝光，很有意思。跟魔法一样！",
        "Thu6": "Hello, @. Wanna watch the TV with me? / 你好，@。想一起看电视吗？",
        "Introduction": "Hmmph... It's irritating to have to meet all these new people, huh? / 哼……要跟这些新面孔打交道还真是不爽啊。#$b#Name's George, by the way. Now buzz off... Hmmph. / 对了，我叫乔治。赶紧给我消失……哼。",
        "Mon": "I'm not much of a talker. Especially not to strangers, if you don't mind me saying. / 我不是很爱说话。尤其不喜欢跟陌生人说话。请别介意。",
        "Wed10_inlaw_Alex": "I'll admit, I thought it was... strange... for two men to be together. But you're such a nice young man, and I know you two are in love... I've changed my mind. / 我承认，我觉得……两个男人在一起太奇怪了。但是我知道你是个很棒的年轻人，而且我知道你们俩相爱了……我已经改变我的想法了。^You're part of the family, now... and I couldn't be more proud. / 现在你是我们家里的一分子了……我简直太骄傲了。",
        "Wed8": "I wish my legs worked so I could play catch with Alex.$s / 我多希望我的腿好起来，这样就可以和亚历克斯捉迷藏了。$s#$e#That'll never happen.$s / 但那已经是不可能的了。$s",
        "joja_Begin": "So... the old Community Center is gone, huh? Whatever happened to small-town values? It's a shame how times have changed... / 那么……老社区中心没了，是吧？不管小镇的价值观有何变化？时代这么变，都是一种耻辱……",
        "MovieInvitation": "You wanna see a movie with an old geezer like me? ...Well... okay. I'll meet you there. / 你想跟我这样的老头去看电影？……唔……好吧。我们到时候见。",
        "Thu10": "When you get as old as me it's a lot harder to adjust to new things. / 到了我这个年纪就很难再适应新鲜事物了。#$e#One day you'll know what I mean. / 有一天你会懂的。#$e#Go on, enjoy yourself while you're still young. / 趁着年轻好好享受吧。",
        "Fri10": "You know, I really have been a grumpy old man to everyone. But now I feel like I'm softening up like an old ripe fruit. Hehe!$h / 我以前是个脾气暴躁的老头子。但是现在我的脾气变得很好了。呵呵！$h#$e#Take care, son. / 保重吧，小子。^Take care, hun. / 保重吧，亲爱的。",
        "winter_1": "Ohh... It's so cold. / 噢……太冷了。#$e#When you're young the cold doesn't bite as hard. / 年轻人就是抗冻啊。",
        "Sun": "Aren't you cold? They don't make sweaters like they used to. / 你不冷吗？他们不再像以前那样织毛衣了。#$e#*Sigh* / *唉*……",
        "Wed": "Alex is my grandson. Have I told you that already? / 亚历克斯是我的孙子。我跟你说过吗？#$e#Huh? Speak up. / 哈？没关系随意说。",
        "married_Alex": "...Hmmph. / ……哼。^I'd like to become a great-grandpa before I croak. Think you can make that happen? / 我入土之前让我当个曾爷爷，你看行不行？",
        "pamHouseUpgradeAnonymous": "Welp... that new house blocks my view of the river a little... but it sure looks nicer than that old tin can Pam was livin' in. / 哎哟……那个新房子有点遮挡我的河景……但它肯定比潘姆原来住的那个老锡罐好看。",
        "Wed10": "@! Let me turn off this darned television and we can have a little chat.$h / @！别看电视了我们来聊天吧。$h#$e#So what are the young people doing these days? / 现在的年轻人都在玩啥？",
        "Sat": "The weekend is no different than any other time, for me. / 对我来说周末和平时也没什么不同。#$e#That's how it is when you're retired. / 你退休了的话也会一样。",
        "Tue10": "You know, I shouldn't get too depressed about my legs. / 对于我的腿，我不该太悲观的。#$e#I should just be happy that I'm alive.$h / 我该庆幸我还活着。$h",
        "Wed_inlaw_Alex": "How can two men get married? It's unnatural... Hmmph. I guess I'm just \"old fashioned\"... / 两个男人怎么可以结婚呢？太不正常了……哼。可能是我“跟不上时代”了……^You're part of the family, now. I'm glad that my grandson found such a nice wife. / 现在你是我们家里的一分子了。我很高兴我的孙子娶到了这么好的妻子。",
        "Fri": "So you're a farmer, huh? At least it's honest work. / 所以你是位农民，是吧？至少是个本分的工作。",
        "pamHouseUpgrade": "Thanks for replacing that beat up old trailer... the new house is much nicer to look at. / 谢谢你换掉那辆破烂不堪的旧拖车……新房子更好看了。#$e#You know, I'll bet it increases the value of our property too! / 你知道吗，我敢确信，这也会增加我们房产的价值！",
        "Fri4": "My grand-pap was a farmer. It's a respectable profession. / 我的爷爷也是农夫。这是个令人尊敬的职业。#$e#If I wasn't so darned old I'd come to your farm and show you a thing or two... / 如果我年轻一点我就去你的农场指点你几招了。",
        "eventSeen_18_memory_oneweek": "I may seem out of touch, but when you've been around for as long as I have, you learn a thing or two about the ways of life. It's called 'wisdom'. / 你看我可能跟不上时代，但你要是到我这个年纪，就能对人生看得透彻了。这就叫“智慧”。#$b#Young people don't understand the big picture. How could they? / 年轻人根本看不清大局。他们哪来这个水平？",
        "eventSeen_502969_memory_oneweek": "I dunno what you did, but those raccoons haven't been back since last week! / 上周之后那个浣熊就再也没来了！不知道你干了什么。"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/Gil",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "Snoring": "...*snore*... / ……*打鼾*……",
        "ComeBackLater": "...Come back when you've got something to show me, kid. / ……孩子，等你有了能让我刮目相看的东西，再来找我吧。"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/Gus",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "Saloon8": "Hi there @. I'm glad to see you! You're always welcome here. / 嗨，@。见到你真高兴！在这儿，你永远是受欢迎的。",
        "GreenRain_2": "*sniff*... These rains have a particular smell. Have you noticed? Almost like freshly minced herbs... / （闻了一下）……这场雨有一股特别的味道，你闻到了吗？像是刚切碎的药草……",
        "cropMatured_256": "Lewis tells me your tomatoes have ripened. That's great news! / 刘易斯跟我说你种的番茄已经成熟了，那真是太好了！#$b#...Just imagine what the culinary world would be like without tomatoes... / ……假如美食界没有番茄，那可太惨了……",
        "divorced_once": "Hey, I'm sorry to hear about the break-up...$s / 哎，听说你离婚了，我很遗憾……$s#$e#If you need company, you're always welcome at the Saloon. / 欢迎多来酒吧，这里有人陪你。",
        "GreenRain": "I saw the weather report last night. It really gave me a scare!$s / 我昨晚看了天气预报，给我吓了一跳！$s#$e#Are there monsters out there? What's happening? / 外面有怪物吗？发生什么事了？",
        "Saloon_Tue": "Hi! Please relax and enjoy yourself. / 嗨！在这里不要拘束哦。",
        "Resort_Entering": "Hey, @! Glad you're here. I'm gonna be serving up some good stuff from behind the bar. / 嘿，@！你能来真好。我负责酒吧，会做很多好喝的。",
        "Resort": "Meet me at the bar if you need a beverage. / 如果你想喝饮料的话，可以到酒吧找我。",
        "Thu": "Pam and Clint come into the saloon almost every night. / 潘姆和克林特几乎每晚都来酒吧。#$e#I'd probably go out of business if they stopped coming.$h / 假如他们不来我就要关门了！$h#$e#So make sure you don't drive them away! / 所以可千万别把他们赶跑了！",
        "divorced_twice": "Another failed marriage? Well, it happens. Guess I'll be seeing you at the Saloon more often...$s / 又经历了一次失败的婚姻吗？唉，有些事情确实无法避免。感觉之后会经常在酒吧见到你了……$s",
        "AcceptGift_(O)StardropTea": "Oh wow, thank you! I'm tempted to drink all of it, but I'm going to save some for the saloon. I bet I could make an interesting cocktail with this! / 哇，谢谢你！我很想一下子喝完，不过还得留一点给酒吧，我肯定能用这个做出一款独特的鸡尾酒！",
        "Saloon": "Welcome to the Stardrop Saloon! Can I get you anything? / 晚上好。需要点什么？",
        "Tue": "I sell different dishes each week, so make sure and check in every now and then! / 我每周都做不一样的菜哦，所以没事就过来看看吧！#$e#You might taste something spectacular.$h / 没准能吃到极品美食哦。$h#$e#Just let me know if you have any allergies.$s / 有忌口的话尽管告诉我。$s#$e#Okay, see you around. / 好的，回头见。",
        "accept_865": "*sniff* sniff* ... that sharp smell! / （嗅、嗅）……这刺鼻的气味！#$b#*slurp* *slurp* ... that zesty taste! That gritty texture! / （咕噜咕噜）……这热情的味道！这粗糙的质感！#$b#It can only be gourmet tomato salt! I'll trade you for it. / 只能是美食家番茄盐了！我来跟你做个交易吧。",
        "AcceptGift_Positive_category_cooking": "*sniff*... Ah. Exquisite cuisine. You know what I like, @.$h / （闻了一下）……啊，真是美味佳肴。@，你很懂我喜欢的东西嘛。$h",
        "Thu6": "Clint comes into the saloon almost every night and sits at the same table by himself. / 克林特每晚都来酒吧，自己一个人，坐的也是同一张桌子。#$e#Sometimes he glances over at Emily with a nervous look. Hmmm. / 有时会紧张的看向艾米丽的方向。嗯……#$e#Maybe that's why he comes in so often. Oh well, that means more business for me. / 这就是他常来的原因吧。哦，这也给我带来了不少生意。",
        "Introduction": "Well hello there! I'm Gus, chef and owner of the Stardrop Saloon. / 你好！我是格斯，星果酒吧的老板兼主厨。#$e#Stop in if you need any refreshments. I've always got hot coffee and cold beer at the ready.$h / 需要提神的话可以光临我的店。这里有的是热咖啡和冰啤酒。$h",
        "Mon": "Yeah, I know a lot about the people living here. / 是啊，我对这里的人很熟。#$e#That's one of the benefits of being a bartender.$h / 这就是酒保的优势。$h#$e#Sometimes I hear too much... / 我听过的故事可多了去了……",
        "SeedShop_Entry": "Hi, Pierre!/Now, what do I need.../Ah, that looks good!/Makin' my special sauce tonight!/Pierre! What's fresh?/Pierre! Waddya got for me? / 嗨，皮埃尔！/嗯，现在需要什么呢……/啊，那个看上去不错！/今晚做我的特制酱汁！/皮埃尔！有什么新产品吗？/皮埃尔！你给我带什么来了？",
        "GreenRainFinished": "I'm glad that's over. Running the saloon is enough to worry about, I don't need exotic weather in my life! / 幸好都结束了，开酒吧的事情已经很多了，可别给我整什么诡异天气了！",
        "Saloon_Thu": "Hey, you look like you could use a beverage. / 嘿，来点喝的吧。",
        "dating_Emily_memory_oneweek": "Emily has a real pep in her step lately... I wonder why? *wink* / 艾米丽最近精神得不得了……你们怎么了？（眨眨眼）",
        "Sun": "Business has been pretty steady thanks to my regular customers. / 最近生意很稳定，真是多亏我的老顾客啊。",
        "Wed": "Emily's been working here for a while now. I don't know what I'd do without her! / 艾米丽在这工作一段时间了。没有她我真不知道该怎么办！#$e#I would hate to have to clean all those pots by myself.$s / 我可不想自己去刷锅。$s",
        "willyCrabs": "These might be the best crab cakes I've ever made... / 这些可能是我烹的最好的蟹肉饼了……",
        "Thu8": "Pam comes into the saloon almost every night and drinks way too much beer. / 潘姆每晚都来酒吧喝很多啤酒。#$e#Ah well, I shouldn't pass judgment on my customers. / 哦对了，我不该过多谈论顾客的事。",
        "pamHouseUpgradeAnonymous": "I saw Pam earlier today... she was grinning from ear to ear! She said someone bought her a new house! / 我今天早些时候遇见了潘姆……她正咧豁了嘴大笑！她说有人给她买了一间新房子！#$e#Whoever it was, they truly deserve the best!$h / 不管是谁，他们真的值得最美的赞扬！$h",
        "Sat": "Are you much of a chef, @? / 你厨艺怎么样，@？#$e#If you have a kitchen and some recipes, you can cook some useful dishes. / 如果有厨房和菜谱，你就可以做出美味的料理啦。#$e#Home-cooked meals make great gifts, as well. / 亲手烹饪的料理也是很好的礼物哦。",
        "eventSeen_502969": "It's important to me that people can eat healthy, delicious meals. Unfortunately, in today's world, that's not so easy for everyone. / 大家能吃上健康美味的饭菜，这是我重要的心愿，很遗憾这对一些人来说还是一件奢侈的事情。",
        "Fri": "Hi there, @. If you're ever thirsty, the Saloon is the place to be. / 你好啊！@。你要是口渴，可以去酒吧。",
        "pamHouseUpgrade": "Hey. I heard what you did for Pam. That was really really nice of you!$h / 嘿。我听说了你为潘姆做的事情。你真是大……大的好人！$h#$e#Sadly, I don't think it will get her to cut back on the 'beverages'... / 可悲的是，我认为这不会让她少喝“饮料”……",
        "married": "Hey @, just want to say that I'm happy for you and %spouse. / 你好啊，@，希望你和%spouse能过得开心。",
        "Resort_Leaving": "I'll see you back home, @. / 回星露谷再见，@。",
        "Saloon4": "Hi there, @. Make yourself at home. / 你好啊，@，请别拘束。",
        "Saloon_Fri": "Business has been really good tonight. I'm pleased. / 今晚的生意很不错。我很高兴。",
        "eventSeen_3206194": "Hey, you really pulled through with those eggs. The omelet turned out great, thanks to you! / 哎，你送来的蛋真是帮了大忙，能做出完美的煎蛋卷，你是大功臣！",
        "Fri4": "I don't actually drink very much myself. I'm mainly doing this to make a living. / 我自己平时不太喝酒。我开酒吧只是为了生计。#$e#Although I do enjoy a taste of the Stardew Valley vintage from time to time. / 不过我也确实很享受星露谷陈酿的香醇。",
        "IslandSouth_14_21": "Hey, need a drink? I've got some special beverages that showcase local ingredients from this island.$h / 嘿，来喝一杯吗？我使用岛上的特殊食材做了一些特别的饮料。$h"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/Haley",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "Event_beach2": "*sigh*$s / *唉*$s#$b#...Maybe it'll wash up on another shore. I can't bear to think of it at the bottom of the ocean.$s / ……或许会被冲到别的海岸去吧。要是沉到海底我得哭死了。$s",
        "summer_Tue2": "Do you wear those clothes every day? / 你每天都穿那一套衣服吗？",
        "Mon6": "I used to complain about this town being so small, but I've grown to like it. / 我以前老是抱怨这个镇太小了，但是我越来越喜欢它了。#$e#If it was much bigger it wouldn't feel like a community. / 假如太大的话，就不会有归属感了。",
        "eventSeen_11_memory_twoweeks": "Did you see last night's episode of 'Tears'? *sob*... I can't believe Kyle and Amy broke up...$s / 你看昨晚播的那集《泪水》了吗？呜呜……卡尔和埃米居然分手了……$s",
        "summer_Tue4": "$p 47#Hey I found this new tool to open jars with. So you won't need to help me anymore.$h / 嘿，我找到了这个开罐头的工具。所以不需要你帮忙啦！$h|There's not a cloud in the sky today.$h / 今天好晴朗，万里无云。$h",
        "Resort_Entering": "I saw a dolphin on the way in! / 我来的时候看见海豚了！",
        "winter_Mon8": "I wish it were warmer here in Stardew Valley. / 星露谷要是能暖和一些就好了。#$e#I could move somewhere else, but... / 我可以搬到别的地方，但是……",
        "Resort_Towel_2": "Laying out on a tropical beach. / 躺在热带海滩上……#$b#*sigh* I think I've finally found my place in the universe. / 唉……我想我终于在宇宙中找到了自己的位置。#$e#But I guess Stardew Valley's not such a bad place either!$h / 但我觉得星露谷也是个不错的地方！$h",
        "Thu": "#$1 HaleyClothes#I've decided I am going to organize my clothes today. I'll have to throw out all of last year's styles to make room for the new ones! / #$1 HaleyClothes#我决定了，今天我把我的衣服整理整理。我要把去年的款式都扔了给新款腾出空间！#$e#*sigh* I could really go for a cupcake right now. / *唉*我好想去吃小蛋糕啊。#$e#Do you need something? / 你有什么需要的么？",
        "married_Emily": "Well, I guess this makes you my 'brother-in-law', huh? That's funny to think about. / 所以你现在是我的姐夫是吧？想想还挺有趣的。^Hey, I guess we're kind of like sisters now!$h / 哎，我们这样就能算姐妹啦！$h",
        "Resort_Towel_3": "Emily's friend had this swimsuit shipped to me from all the way out in Zuzu City. / 这件泳衣是艾米丽的朋友从祖祖城寄给我的。#$e#City fashion is on a whole different level, isn't it?$h / 大城市的时尚层次就是不一样，是不是？$h",
        "Sat8": "#$1 haleySeagull#Yesterday I found a seagull with her wing caught in a net. I set her free, of course. She looked so helpless, the poor thing. / 昨天我发现一只翅膀被网缠住的海鸥。当然，我把它给放了。它看起来好无助，可怜的小东西。$k$s#$e#You know, I should probably start exercising more... this youthful metabolism won't last forever. / 或许我应该多锻炼锻炼了……永葆青春什么的毕竟都是异想天开啊。",
        "Event_darkroom6": "Is that so...?$s / 是这样吗……？$s",
        "summer_Thu": "If you stay in the sun a lot it'll make your hair lighter. / 如果经常晒太阳会使你头发更亮。#$e#It's a good thing to know! / 这是好事哦！",
        "summer_Sat_13": "What? You'd better not be doing that!$a / 什么？你最好别有这个想法！$a",
        "summer_Fri10": "Oh, hi @! / 啊，你好啊，@！#$e#Do you like kids?$l / 你喜欢小孩子吗？$l",
        "winter_Sat8": "I'm glad you have less work to do in the winter. / 冬天你就不用太操劳了，真是挺好呢。#$e#It must be nice to have a break, huh? / 能休息一下很不错吧？",
        "Thu6": "I cooked dinner last night. It actually turned out okay! / 我昨晚做了晚餐。感觉还不错！#$e#But I did make a huge mess in the kitchen... / 但是我把厨房搞得一团糟……",
        "fall_1": "It's fall already?$s / 已经是秋天了？$s",
        "Resort_Shore_2": "Wow, look at how the sunlight sparkles on the horizon!$h / 哇哦，看看地平线上的阳光多么耀眼！$h#$b#I bet the sunsets here would make for an amazing photo. / 这里的日落肯定可以拍出惊艳的照片。#$e#I have to remember to bring my camera next time. / 下次来得记得带上相机。",
        "fall_Tue": "Hmm... Something smells weird... / 嗯……有奇怪的气味……#$e#You've been working on the farm, huh? / 你一直都在农场工作，是吧？",
        "summer_10": "Do you have baby bunnies on your farm? Bunnies are SO cute! < / 你的农场有小兔子吗？小兔子好可爱！<",
        "Introduction": "Oh... you're that new farmer boy, aren't you? / 噢……你就是那个新来的农夫吧？^Oh... You're that new farmer girl, or whatever. Aren't you? / 噢……你就是那个新来的农场姑娘吧？#$e#Huh? Oh... I'm Haley. / 哈？噢……我是海莉。#$e#Hmm... If it weren't for those horrendous clothes you might actually be cute. / 嗯……要不是你那身衣服，你应该还挺可爱的吧。^Hmm... If it weren't for those horrendous clothes you might actually be pretty... Actually, never mind.$h / 嗯……要不是你那身衣服，你应该还挺漂亮的吧。……呃，别介意。$h",
        "eventSeen_12_memory_twoweeks": "My parents sent another postcard... I guess they're in the middle of a cruise down the Gem Sea Coast. / 我爸妈又寄来了一张明信片……估计他们在坐邮轮经过宝石海岸。#$e#They said me and Emily could join them at any point, but let's be honest... who wants to go on vacation with their parents? / 他们说我和艾米丽随时都可以去，但说实话……谁想跟父母一起度假呢？",
        "cropMatured_421": "My name means 'field of hay', but I like to imagine it as a meadow full of sunflowers... / 我的名字意思是“干草地”，但我更喜欢把它想象成开满向日葵的草地……",
        "summer_Sat": "Farming sounds so boring...#$q 42/43 summer_Sat_old#What do you even do all day?#$r 42 10 summer_Sat_12#Care for plants#$r 42 10 summer_Sat_12#Explore the caves#$r 43 -10 summer_Sat_13#Snoop around in your room#$r 42 10 summer_Sat_12#Dig for treasure / 农场的活好像很无聊的样子……#$q 42/43 summer_Sat_old#一天都干什么呢？#$r 42 10 summer_Sat_12#护理植物#$r 42 10 summer_Sat_12#探索山洞#$r 43 -10 summer_Sat_13#在房子里面转#$r 42 10 summer_Sat_12#挖宝藏",
        "Mon": "This town is so small. It sucks.$u / 小镇太小了。没意思。$u#$e#I have to drive, like, twenty miles to buy any decent clothes.$s / 我得开车去，大概，20 英里去买得体的服装。$s#$e#That's why I usually just order online. / 这就是为什么我一般网购。#$e#What? / 什么？",
        "secondChance_Girls": "Alright, alright... I'm done giving you the cold shoulder. Just promise me you'll never, ever lie to me again.$s / 好吧，好吧……我不想再给你冷脸看了。只要答应我，你永远不会再对我撒谎。$s",
        "FlowerDance_Decline": "Ew... No. / 额……不。",
        "fall_Wed4": "If you're ever bored, come say hi. / 要是无聊了，就过来打个招呼吧。",
        "Event_darkroom4": "Aw, thanks!$h / 啊，谢谢！$h",
        "fall_Wed": "Oh, hi. Did you want something? / 嗨。想要点什么？",
        "Fri2": "Don't you get tired of running around on that farm all day, or whatever it is you do? / 你成天在农场忙活来忙活去，就不觉得无聊吗？#$e#I couldn't stand getting all dirty like that. / 浑身弄得脏兮兮的，我可忍不了。#$e#You probably get a nice tan, though. / 你的皮肤一定已经晒成小麦色了吧？",
        "Wed": "The only thing I like about this town is the beach.$u / 我唯一喜欢这小镇的就是海滩。$u",
        "AcceptGift_(O)421": "Wow, they're beautiful! These are my absolute favorite.$h / 哇，好漂亮啊！我最喜欢这个了。$h",
        "dumped_Girls": "I've got nothing to say to you!$a / 我对你没什么好说的！$a",
        "Event_room2": "What? That sounds fun, but I wouldn't want to leave Stardew Valley right now... / 什么？好像很好玩的样子，但我现在不想离开星露谷……",
        "divorced_Emily": "Things didn't work out between you and Emily, huh? Well... It happens. / 看来你跟艾米丽合不来啊？唉……也是常有的事。#$e#It *is* kind of awkward that you're both still living in this tiny town, though. / 而且住在小镇上抬头不见低头见的，确实挺尴尬。",
        "Event_darkroom5": "Oh! I thought you knew. / 噢！我还以为你知道呢。#$b#This room's for developing photos. / 这屋子是用来洗相片的。",
        "fall_Sat": "It's too cold to go to the beach anymore.#$q 44 fall_Sat_old#*sigh*...what do you think I should do today?#$r 44 10 fall_Sat_12#Watercolor painting#$r 44 20 fall_Sat_12#Relax and read a magazine#$r 44 -30 fall_Sat_13#Stop being a selfish crybaby / 现在去海滩太冷了。#$q 44 fall_Sat_old#*唉*……你觉得我今天做点什么好呢？#$r 44 10 fall_Sat_12#水彩画#$r 44 20 fall_Sat_12#阅读杂志#$r 44 -30 fall_Sat_13#安安静静的呆着",
        "Resort_Chair": "I painted my toenails blue to match the sea. What do you think? *wiggle* *wiggle*$h / 我把脚趾甲涂成了蓝色，这样就能和大海相衬了。你觉得怎么样？（扭扭）$h",
        "eventSeen_14": "It was fun taking pictures, but I had to shower for two hours to get the mud out of my hair!$h / 拍照真的很开心，但是后来我洗了两个小时的澡才把头发里的泥巴洗干净！$h",
        "winter_Fri": "Do you have a pony on your farm?$h / 你的农场上有小马吗？$h#$e#Oh. That's disappointing...$s / 噢。好失望……$s",
        "fall_Mon10": "@, I'm happy to see you today.$h / @，今天很高兴见到你。$h",
        "winter_Sun": "Will you say hi to Alex for me? / 你能帮我去跟亚历克斯打个招呼吗？#$e#Thanks. / 谢谢你。",
        "summer_Sat_12": "Hmm... sounds like a lot of work. / 嗯……听起来是个大工程。",
        "GreenRain": "I don't think I've ever set foot in this place. It's actually kind of cozy!$h / 我好像还没来过这里，还挺舒服的！$h#$e#Oh, I'm not worried about the rain. I'm sure it'll pass. / 啊，我不是很担心这场雨，肯定会停的。",
        "Event_jar1": "Great, then you shouldn't have any problem opening this jar for me!$h / 太好了，那你帮我打开这个罐头应该没问题！$h",
        "Event_darkroom1": "Aw, thanks!$h / 啊，谢谢！$h",
        "fall_Mon": "It's gross when all these fallen leaves get slimy. / 很明显了，落叶都变的黏糊糊了。",
        "summer_Fri4": "I spent 3 hours practicing my signature today. / 我今天花了 3 小时练习签名。#$e#I guess that's pretty silly, huh? / 是不是很傻？",
        "breakUp": "Agh!$8 / 啊！$8#$b#Oh... hmph. Beat me to it, huh? Alright... / 哦……唔。抢在我前头提出来，是吧？真有你的……",
        "AcceptGift_(O)StardropTea": "For me? Ooooh... I can't decide if I should drink it, or use it as shampoo... / 送我的？欸……不知道是应该喝了，还是用来洗头发……",
        "winter_Sun10": "@, you look rugged today. I like it. / @，你今天精神不错啊，我喜欢。^@, you look pretty today. / @，你今天很漂亮嘛。#$e#...$h / ……$h",
        "summer_Wed4": "It's so hot today! / 今天好热！#$e#I wish I had some ice cream.$s / 希望可以吃到冰淇淋。$s",
        "summer_Tue": "Ew, you're all dirty. / 咦，你们好脏。",
        "winter_Fri8": "Do you think you'll ever have a pony on your farm? / 你的农场会养小马吗？",
        "fall_Tue2": "Something smells earthy... / 有泥土的味道……#$b#Oh, right. You work on a farm. / 哦，对。你在农场工作。",
        "winter_Sat": "The only good thing about winter is that I get to sleep more. / 冬天的唯一好处就是我可以多睡一会。#$e#I like at least 10 hours of sleep every night. / 我每天晚上要睡 10 小时。",
        "fall_Sat_13": "Get away from me, you stupid jerk.$a / 离我远点，你这混蛋。$a",
        "summer_Sat6": "It seems like a good day to go swimming. / 看起来是个游泳的好日子。",
        "married_Emily_memory_oneweek": "Is Emily settling into the farm life? / 艾米丽适应农场生活了吗？#$e#You know, I was starting to wonder if Emily would ever get married... / 我跟你说，我之前还在想艾米丽会不会就不结婚了……",
        "Sun6": "I'm thinking about donating a bunch of clothes... I must have a hundred pairs of shoes. / 我想捐一些衣物……我的鞋子估计得有一百来双了。",
        "FlowerDance_Accept": "Oh... you want to dance with *me*, do you?$13 / 啊……你是想邀请本小姐跳舞吗？$13^Oh? Sure! I'll dance with you! / 啊？好呀！我可以跟你跳舞！#$b#Hehe... of course. I'd love to be your partner.$h / 嘻嘻……当然可以，我很乐意做你的舞伴。$h^We'll have a great time!$h / 我们玩个痛快吧！$h#$e#Hmm... I admire your confidence. Most guys are too shy to ask me. / 唔……你挺自信的，我很欣赏。其他男生太害羞了，都不敢邀请我。^You look so pretty today!$h / 你今天真的好漂亮！$h",
        "Resort_Shore": "It's strange the places life can take you... who knows what other lands are out there? / 活久了总是能见到各种奇特的地方……谁知道在此之外的地方又是什么样呢？",
        "Event_clean3": "She should take the 'high road'? What's that supposed to mean?$u / “避开麻烦”？什么意思？$u#$b#You think I'm being a baby, huh?%fork$a / 你觉得我好骗，是吧？%fork$a",
        "Event_darkroom3": "Is that so...?$s / 是这样吗……？$s",
        "summer_Sun": "Emily usually cooks dinner... But she makes weird stuff like quinoa. / 一般是艾米丽做晚餐……但是她用的都是藜麦之类的奇怪食材。",
        "fall_Sun": "I've never been to the forest. It's muddy and I could get a blister on my foot. / 我从未去过树林。那里很泥泞，而且我的脚可能会起水泡。",
        "winter_9": "Hmm. What brand is your shirt? / 唔，你的衬衫是什么牌子的？#$e#Oh. Um, never mind. / 噢。呃，没什么。",
        "fall_Sat_old": "I'll probably take a nap later. / 我一会大概要去小憩一下。",
        "eventSeen_11_memory_oneweek": "The other day, Emily baked something called a 'squirrel loaf'...$u / 前几天，艾米丽烤了一个东西，她说叫“松鼠面包”……$u#$e#How'd it taste? Um... well, if my tail was a little bushier I probably would've loved it.$h / 味道么，呃……如果我真有毛茸茸的尾巴，或许会喜欢吧。$h",
        "winter_Thu": "I'm going to start writing a list of all the clothes I need for next spring. / 我要开始写一份明年春天我需要的衣服清单。",
        "AcceptBirthdayGift_Loved": "*gasp*... You got this for me? Wow, @, this is the best birthday gift ever!$h / 嘶……这是送我的吗？哇，@，这是我收到的最棒的生日礼物！$h",
        "fall_Tue8": "I'm starting to like the smell of dirt. Isn't that weird? / 我开始喜欢泥土的气息了。很奇怪不是吗？#$e#I think it's because you're around all the time.$h / 我觉得可能是因为你经常在附近晃悠。$h",
        "Event_beach1": "No, you won't! This bracelet was passed down to me by my great-grandmother!$a / 不，不行！这手镯是我的曾祖母传下来的！$a",
        "Event_jar2": "Oh... you aren't? Hmmm...$s / 哦……你不是？唔……$s#$b#Well could you try opening this jar for me anyways? / 那你能帮我打开这个罐头吗？",
        "fall_Thu": "I feel the urge to go shopping. *sigh* / 我好想去买买买啊。*唉*",
        "GreenRain_2": "Wake me up when there's a pink rain... Or better yet, a pink cake rain! / 假如下粉色的雨再叫醒我吧……能下粉色的蛋糕雨那就更好了！",
        "winter_Wed": "I wish someone would bring me a peppermint coffee.$s / 真希望有人能给我带杯薄荷味的咖啡。$s#$e#Don't even bother, I know you won't be able to make one. / 不用麻烦了，我知道你做不出来。",
        "winter_Wed6": "I think I'm starting to realize that clothes aren't the most important thing. Right? / 我好像开始明白了，衣服并不是最重要的。你说是吧？#$e#I still like clothes, though. I mean, what's wrong with expressing yourself a little? / 不过我还是很喜欢衣服。稍微打扮一下自己有什么不好呢？",
        "Tue2": "I wonder if any nice shells washed up on the beach this morning? / 今早海滩会有美丽的贝壳被冲上来吗？#$e#This isn't the best time of year for shells, though. / 虽然现在不是一年中捡贝壳的最好时节。",
        "Resort": "This is such a perfect beach. I'd stay here forever if I could! / 真是完美的海滩。要是可以的话，我愿意永远待在这里！",
        "Event_clean2": "NO!! I'm not going to do it!$a / 不！！！我才不要！$a#$b#You guys are both stupid!%fork$a / 你俩都是大笨蛋！%fork$a",
        "Event_clean1": "*sigh*...$u / *唉*……$u",
        "dating_Haley_memory_oneyear": "So, what's the idea here... am I just going to be your 'girlfriend' forever...?$7 / 所以你想怎么样……要我就这么一直当你的“女朋友”吗？$7",
        "summer_Mon6": "I should start reading some books instead of magazines. / 我应该放下杂志，开始看书了。#$e#It's good to learn things, isn't it? / 学习些新知识很棒吧？#$e#I only ever look at the pictures. / 我一般都只看图。",
        "Wed8": "There are only two things I like about this town. / 这个小镇，有两点是我喜欢的。#$b#One of them is the beach. / 一个是海滩。#$e#The other one is a secret! *giggle*$h / 另一个保密！* 咯咯笑 *$h",
        "Event_darkroom2": "Oh! I thought you knew. / 噢！我还以为你知道呢。#$b#This room's for developing photos. / 这屋子是用来洗相片的。",
        "winter_Tue": "Hi. Do you need something from me? / 嗨。有什么需要的吗？#$e#... / ……",
        "winter_Tue4": "Hi @. / 嗨，@。#$e#Is anything exciting happening on your farm? / 农场上有什么好玩的事吗？",
        "Event_room1": "Him? No! / 他？不！#$b#...Well, I guess I used to like Alex. But not anymore! He's immature. / ……我以前确实喜欢过亚历克斯。但是现在不喜欢了！他太不成熟了。",
        "Fri10": "@, can we go on a camping trip someday? / @，我们有空去野营吧？#$e#The most exotic place I've been is Zuzu city. / 我去过的最怪异的地方就是祖祖城了。",
        "Sun": "My sister is so weird. Sometimes I wonder if we're actually related.$u / 我姐姐好奇怪。有时候我都怀疑我们是否有血缘关系。$u",
        "eventSeen_12_memory_oneweek": "Wow, looks like someone's read the latest issue of 'Super Fashion Girl'... muddy boots are totally in right now!$h / 哇，好像有人读过了最新一期的《超级时尚女孩》……沾了泥巴的靴子现在超流行！$h",
        "winter_Sun6": "Um, if you see Alex could you tell him I'm busy today? / 嗯，你要是见到亚历克斯，麻烦跟他说声我今天很忙，好吗？#$e#Thanks. / 谢谢你。",
        "divorced": "I'll be fine on my own...$7 / 我自己挺好……$7#$e#Thanks for the memories.$7 / 谢谢你给我的这些回忆。$7#$e#Why are you still clinging to me? Go live your own life.$7 / 你还赖着我干嘛？去过你自己的日子吧。$7",
        "AcceptGift_(O)88": "$c 0.8#Is that... coconut? I love this!$h#Mmm.... coconuts remind me of warm, sunny days at the beach. When I hold one, I feel like I'm there... even when it's raining. / $c 0.8#这个是椰子吧？我超喜欢的！$h#让我想起了在海滩上玩的时候，天气温暖，阳光明媚，拿着这个感觉身临其境……",
        "Fri6": "I need to find some kind of hobby other than shopping. / 我得找找除了购物之外的爱好了。#$e#I've decided I want to expand my horizons. / 我得开阔下眼界。#$e#Maybe I should learn to play the mini-harp? / 也许我该学学迷你竖琴？",
        "Event_room3": "Huh? What's an android? / 哈？机器人是什么？",
        "winter_Thu6": "Maybe I'll donate some of my skirts to a charity this spring. / 也许今年春天我要捐出一些裙子。#$e#I mean, I do have over 1,000 skirts.$h / 我估摸我现在得有 1000 多条裙子了。$h#$e#...what? / ……什么？",
        "summer_Fri": "I wonder what Alex is doing today... / 亚历克斯今天在干什么呢……#$e#Huh? I didn't notice you standing there. / 啊？我没注意你在这。",
        "fall_Thu6": "Shopping just doesn't sound as fun as it used to. / 购物不像以前那么有趣了。#$e#What's happening to me? / 我这是怎么了？#$e#Hmm... / 唔……",
        "summer_Sun6": "#$1 HaleySister#I talked to my sister for a while last night. I actually enjoyed it quite a bit. / #$1 HaleySister#我昨晚和我姐姐聊了一会。聊得很开心。#$e#You know, Emily's not actually that weird. I guess we have more in common than I used to think. / 其实艾米丽没那么古怪的。我们有很多共同点。#$e#Don't tell her I said so. / 别告诉她我说的。",
        "Tue": "Nice shoes. / 不错的鞋子。^Nice makeup. / 不错的样式。#$b#Are those made out of plastic? / 是用塑料做的吗？^Or wait... Are you even wearing any? / 哦等等……你穿了？#$e#I'm bored. / 我好无聊。",
        "AcceptBirthdayGift_Negative": "Gross! You got me this on my birthday? What's wrong with you!$a / 好恶心！我生日你就送我这个？你在搞什么东西！$a",
        "fall_Sat_12": "Hmm... That's a pretty good idea, actually. / 嗯……是个好主意。",
        "FlowerDance_Accept_Spouse": "*sigh*... My days of being Flower Queen are over... so it's a bittersweet dance for me.$s / *唉*……我是花女王的时代已经结束了……所以对我来说这是一次苦乐参半的舞蹈。$s#$b#But, yes... / 但是，是的……",
        "summer_Wed": "Um... Yes? / 呃……怎么了？#$e#I didn't hear you, I'm thinking about something else. / 我没听见。刚刚想别的事了。",
        "fall_Mon6": "$p 48#Did I ever tell you I found another one of my great-grandma's bracelets in the attic? / 我有没有跟你说过我在阁楼上找到了我曾祖母的另一个手镯？|See this bracelet? It belonged to my great-grandmother. / 看到这个镯子了吗？是我曾祖母的。#$e#She was a really interesting lady. / 她是位很有意思的女士。",
        "Resort_Towel": "Getting the perfect tan is an art form... / 要晒成完美的棕褐色皮肤是一门艺术活……#$e#It's kind of like toasting a marshmallow... you have to rotate the body just right.$h / 有点像烤棉花糖……你旋转身体的节奏得刚刚好。$h",
        "dating_Haley": "I was waiting for you to ask me that.$l / 我一直在等你约我呢。$l",
        "summer_Sat_old": "#$p 43#Hey, you better not be snooping around in my room anymore!$a|But I guess it could get you in pretty good shape. / #$p 43#嘿，你最好别在我房间里偷偷摸摸的！！$a|不过我估计你没准能练出个好身材。",
        "summer_Mon": "I'm going to get such a nice tan this summer. / 我今年夏天要好好晒下太阳，晒出小麦色皮肤。",
        "Wed4": "I'm glad that the flowers are starting to bloom. / 这些花终于要开了。#$e#Those pink ones smell so good.$h / 那些粉色的好香。$h",
        "AcceptBirthdayGift_Liked": "Awwwww, you got me a birthday gift? Well, I really like it!$h / 哇，你给我准备生日礼物了？我很喜欢！$h",
        "fall_Fri": "Is that a grass stain on your knee? / 你膝盖上是草的痕迹吗？#$e#Sorry, I'm allergic to grass. / 不好意思，我对青草过敏。",
        "fall_Fri4": "You look like you've been doing a lot of hard work. / 你好像忙坏了啊。#$b#Why don't you take the rest of the day off? / 为什么不休息一下呢？",
        "summer_Tue8": "I guess living in the country isn't so bad. / 我觉得居住在乡下也不是很糟糕。#$e#If I lived in the city I might start to miss all the trees. / 如果我住在城市里就看不到这么多树了。#$e#@, I think I've been hanging out with you too much.$h / @，我感觉最近总跟你混在一起，有点耳濡目染了呢。$h",
        "Sat": "I'm feeling an urge to go shopping. Ugh! I wish there was a mall here. / 我好想去买买买啊！啊！真希望能有个大型商场。",
        "fall_Sun6": "I've never been to the forest, you know. / 我都没去过树林呢。#$e#It might be interesting to explore it some day. / 也许以后有空可以去探险。",
        "winter_Mon": "I want to move somewhere warmer. / 我想搬去个暖和点的地方。",
        "Fri": "%Haley is ignoring you. / %海莉没有理你。",
        "dating_Haley_memory_oneday": "You look really handsome today.$l / 你今天真的好帅。$l^You look really pretty today.$l / 你今天真的好漂亮。$l",
        "Resort_Leaving": "There's something about the sun that just makes me feel good. / 晒着太阳莫名地让我觉得很舒服。",
        "winter_Tue2": "Your name is @, right? / 你叫@，对吧？#$e#I keep forgetting. / 我总记不住。",
        "Resort_Bar": "Gus made a cute, fruity drink just for me!$h / 格斯为我特制了一款可爱的果饮！$h",
        "eventSeen_13_memory_oneweek": "%Haley greets you with a smile. You notice that she's wearing her Great-Grandma's bracelet. / %海莉对你笑了一下。你注意到她戴着曾祖母的手镯。",
        "summer_Thu6": "If you stay in the sun a lot it will make your hair lighter... But you don't want to get sunburnt, either. / 如果经常晒太阳会使你头发更亮。但是你不想被晒伤吧。#$e#I just want a healthy amount of sunlight. Everything in moderation, right? / 我只想健康地晒太阳。凡事都有度，不是吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/Harvey",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "Mon6": "I'd like to stay in Stardew Valley for a while. I'm finally starting to feel involved in the community. / 我想在星露谷多待一阵子。我终于感觉开始融入这个集体了。#$e#It feels good to know that you're useful. / 当你感觉自己的存在有价值的时候，你的心情也会很不错。",
        "Resort_Entering": "Sunscreen? Check... / 防晒霜？带了……#$b#Sun hat? Check... / 遮阳帽？带了……",
        "Thu": "Nutrition is important, so make sure and eat well. Try to increase your vegetable intake! / 营养很重要，一定要好好吃饭。尽量多吃蔬菜！#$e#Home-cooked meals are best. Do you cook? / 自家做的饭是最好的。你做饭吗？",
        "summer_Thu": "Exercise is important, but don't get too exhausted, or you might end up at my clinic! / 锻炼是很重要的，但是不要太过火了，不然你就得来我的诊所！#$e#Make sure and listen to your body. / 注意不要太勉强。",
        "event_heart3": "Um. Okay... If you say so.$s / 嗯。好吧……既然你这么说的话。$s",
        "Introduction": "It's a pleasure to meet you. I'm Harvey, the local doctor. / 很高兴认识你。我是哈维，这里的医生。#$e#I perform regular check-ups and medical procedures for all the residents of Pelican Town. It's rewarding work. / 我为鹈鹕镇的居民提供常规的体检和医疗服务。这是个很有意义的工作。#$e#I hope you'll find your own work equally rewarding, in time.$h / 希望有天你也会觉得自己的工作很有意义。$h",
        "Mon": "We sell a few over-the-counter medicines at the clinic... feel free to stop by if you're feeling exhausted. / 我们诊所出售一些非处方药……如果感到疲惫乏力还请来光临。#$b#I know that being a farmer is pretty tiring work... don't overdo it! / 我知道当一名农夫是非常劳累的……不要太勉强哦！",
        "eventSeen_58_memory_fourweeks": "I don't know why I was ashamed about being in dance aerobics class. My legs have become so strong, I should feel as bold as a lion! / 我之前为什么要对参加有氧健身课感到害羞呢……我现在腿部肌肉强壮了很多，感觉自己勇猛无比！",
        "FlowerDance_Decline": "Oh! I'm sorry... I, er... have plans to ask someone else.$s / 噢！不好意思……我，呃……打算邀请别人。$s",
        "Mon10": "Oh! Hi, @.$l / 噢！嗨，@。$l#$e#Do you... have any medical questions?$l / 你……要问诊吗？$l",
        "eventSeen_58_memory_oneweek": "Well now that you know my secret, I might as well give you an update... I was significantly less winded after aerobics class this week! / 既然你都知道我的秘密了，那我再跟你说说……这周的有氧健身课上完，我已经不怎么喘了！",
        "Wed": "Remember to cover your mouth when you sneeze. / 记得打喷嚏的时候用手捂住嘴。#$e#Then make sure to wash your hands. / 然后别忘了洗手。",
        "event_heart1": "Oh! Hospitals make you nervous, huh? / 噢！进了医院你就会紧张是吧？#$b#Just try and relax. I'm here to help.$h / 放松。我一定会帮你的。$h",
        "fall_Sat": "When you eat certain foods you'll perform better. / 常吃某些食物对身体有好处哦。#$e#Eating a 'Farmer's Lunch' will give you the nutrition you need to water and harvest crops better! / 吃“农场主的早午饭”可以让你获取更均衡的营养，满足你浇灌和收割作物时的体力需求！",
        "AcceptBirthdayGift_Positive": "Oh! Thank you very much! I didn't expect anyone to know it was my birthday today.$h / 啊！非常感谢！我没想到会有人知道今天是我的生日。$h",
        "Resort_Chair": "It's nice to have an opportunity to relax now and then. / 能时不时地找到放松的机会，这还挺好的。#$b#The trouble is actually letting go of your worries...$s / 彻底放下你的烦恼才是真正困难的事……$s",
        "Tue8": "$query PLAYER_NPC_RELATIONSHIP current any married roommate#Don't overwork yourself, @. Doctor's orders! / $query PLAYER_NPC_RELATIONSHIP current any married roommate#@，别把自己累坏了，这是医嘱！#$e#If our farmers get sick, where will we get our food? We need you!$h|Don't overwork yourself, @. Doctor's orders! / 要是你病倒了，没了庄稼我们该怎么吃饭？我们需要你！$h|不要过度劳累，@。这是医嘱！#$e#Your health is important to me.$l / 你的健康对我来说很重要。$l",
        "winter_Sun": "I hate to say this, but I do make a lot more money during flu season. / 虽然我不想这么说，但是流感季节我确实多挣很多钱。#$e#I guess if people stopped getting sick, I'd be out of business. / 如果人们不再生病那我也就失业了。#$e#Don't get the wrong idea! I want people to be healthy... really! / 别误会。我真的希望每个人都健健康康！",
        "GreenRain": "I brought some medical supplies, just in case. Be careful out there! / 我带了一些医疗用品以防万一，出门的时候小心点！",
        "breakUp": "...Y...You...?$s / ……你……你……？$s#$b#*gulp*... I... I think I'm going to be sick...$s / （咽口水）……我……我大概是要生病了……$s",
        "AcceptGift_(O)StardropTea": "You're giving me this? I'm honored. Thank you! / 你要送我这个吗？我很荣幸，谢谢你！",
        "Sun6": "Imagine having a patient's life completely in your hands, and failing to keep them alive... that's something that will haunt you forever.$s / 你想想，病人的性命就掌握在你手里，而你没能把他救活……这事情会一直在你心里挥之不去。$s",
        "AcceptGift_(O)432": "It's for me? Thank you! This will be fantastic drizzled on some pasta.$h / 是送给我的吗？谢谢你！这个淋在意大利面上肯定很好吃。$h",
        "FlowerDance_Accept": "Oh! You... want to dance with me?$4 / 啊！你……你想跟我跳舞吗？$4#$b#...Yes. I'd love to!$h / ……好的，我非常愿意！$h",
        "Resort_Shore": "I combed the whole beach for glass. We wouldn't want anyone to get a cut on their foot! / 我检查了整片沙滩，看有没有玻璃。大家都不希望有人被划伤脚的！",
        "Mon2": "I feel responsible for the health of this whole community... it's kind of stressful. / 对全镇的居民健康负责，这是我内心的使命……压力不小。#$e#It's a pretty small community, and I'm fortunate to be able to build a good relationship with my patients. / 我们这里人不多，我很幸运的可以跟我的病人建立良好的关系。",
        "Sat4": "I came here because I liked the small-town atmosphere, and the potential for a holistic approach to patient care. / 我来这是因为我喜欢小镇的氛围，和集体对病人的关怀。#$e#I've grown to really love it.$h / 我真的是越来越喜欢这种氛围了。$h",
        "Wed6": "It's nice to have a friend in town.$h / 在镇子里有个朋友真不错。$h",
        "Thu8": "$query PLAYER_NPC_RELATIONSHIP current any married roommate#As a doctor, I'm well aware of the benefits of home-cooked food. But I'm so busy, I have a hard time bringing myself to cook.$s|It's a lot of work, being a doctor. I don't eat as well as I should.$s / $query PLAYER_NPC_RELATIONSHIP current any married roommate#我自己是医生，我知道自己做饭有很多好处，可是我太忙了，根本没时间做饭。$s|医生有很多工作，很难好好吃上饭。$s#$e#If I didn't live alone I think it would be easier.$l / 如果我不是单身的话应该会好得多。$l",
        "Sat10": "*Sigh*... I'm starting to feel kind of old... / 唉……我开始感觉自己有点老了……#$e#The older you get the more memories you're burdened with. It can be overwhelming.$s / 年纪越大，记着的事情就越多，有可能会不堪重负。$s#$e#I think I'll stay younger with you around.$l / 有你在的时候，我有种变年轻的感觉。$l",
        "dating_Maru_memory_oneday": "Maru's been unusually cheerful lately... I hear you may have something to do with that. / 玛鲁最近特别兴奋……听说跟你有关系。",
        "GreenRain_2": "The first time this happened, we were all worried that the rain might be dangerous. / 第一次下这种雨的时候，我们都担心会很危险。#$b#But what if it's actually healthy for the body? Who knows... The plants seem to respond well to it, at least. / 可是说不准这雨水反而有益健康呢？天知道……至少植物都长势很好。",
        "winter_Wed": "It's flu season, so you'd better be extra careful. / 现在是流感多发季节，最好格外小心。#$e#Make sure to wash your hands often. / 注意经常洗手。",
        "Resort": "I'll let you in on a little secret... I can only swim with floaties.$s / 我要告诉你一个小秘密……我必须戴着救生圈才能游泳。$s",
        "eventSeen_58_memory_twoweeks": "I got such a good workout during aerobics class, I think I can treat myself to some pasta primavera tonight...$h / 有氧健身课的效果真是太好了，我觉得今晚可以奖励自己一顿蔬菜意面……$h",
        "dating_Harvey": "I've never felt like this before...$l / 我是第一次产生这样的感觉……$l",
        "secondChance_Guys": "I want you back in my life, @. I'm willing to forget what happened.$s / 我想让你回到我的生活中，@。我愿意忘记发生过什么。$s",
        "eventSeen_56_memory_fourweeks": "I've been working on an 'animal checklist' for a few years now. I want to observe every species living in the valley! / 这几年我一直在制作“动物清单”——我想观察星露谷里的每一种生物！",
        "event_grave1": "...You're right. / ……你说得对。#$b#...Thanks. / ……谢谢。",
        "Wed8": "You have a really healthy glow. That's good.$h / 你脸色很不错。很好。$h",
        "event_heart2": "Okay. That makes sense. / 好。这样就对了。",
        "Fri10": "Stop by my place if you ever need a confidential check-up.$l / 如果需要体检的话就来我这儿。$l",
        "Sun": "Hmm... I'm struggling to make ends meet. I don't have enough patients. / 嗯……我现在已经要入不敷出了。现在来找我看病的病人不是很多。#$e#I guess I should try to get patients from the neighboring towns... / 我觉得我得试着从邻镇找病人了……",
        "married_Harvey": "This is the happiest moment of my life...$l / 我是第一次产生这样的感觉……$l",
        "event_aerobics1": "Thanks, @. I appreciate that.$h / 谢谢你，@。非常感谢。$h",
        "eventSeen_571102_memory_oneweek": "As a doctor, you can only do so much to help your patients... / 作为医生，能为病人做的只有这么多……#$e#I've made the mistake of getting too emotionally involved in the past... I won't let that happen again...$s / 我以前犯过过度共情的错误……以后再也不会了……$s",
        "divorced": "I... I can't look at you. Please spare me any more pain.$s / 我……我无法再面对你了。求你别让我承受更多的痛苦。$s",
        "married_Maru": "Congratulations on your marriage, @. Maru's already informed me that she'll continue to work at the clinic, which is a relief! / @，祝你新婚快乐。玛鲁已经跟我说了她会留在诊所工作，我听到的时候真是松了一口气！",
        "event_aerobics2": "*Sigh*... rude.$s / *唉*……过分。$s",
        "dating_Harvey_memory_oneday": "I've been thinking about you so much, I can hardly do my work.$l / 我想你想得都快没法工作了。$l",
        "summer_Fri": "People don't get sick much during the summer. That's nice, but it also means less business for me. / 夏天人们很少生病。好倒是很好，但也意味着我没有多少生意了。",
        "Fri4": "If you want to hang out in my apartment, that's okay with me. I live above the clinic. / 如果你想去我的公寓里逛逛，没问题。我住在诊所上面。",
        "Tue": "Feel free to stop by my office if you're ever feeling ill. / 如果感觉生病了请尽管来我办公室。#$e#You're young, though. You'll probably stay healthy without trying.$h / 当然，你还年轻。身体不用怎么保护也会很健康的。$h",
        "AcceptBirthdayGift_Negative": "Oh! It's a... well, it's something. I didn't expect anyone to know it was my birthday today. / 啊！这个……呃，聊胜于无吧。我没想到会有人知道今天是我的生日。",
        "event_grave2": "*sigh*$s / *唉*$s",
        "FlowerDance_Accept_Spouse": "I've been looking forward to it all afternoon! You look radiant in the fresh spring air, my love.$l / 我都等了一个下午了！在春天清新的气息中，你真是光芒四射啊，亲爱的。$l",
        "AcceptGift_(O)348": "For me? What a gift! This looks fantastic!$h / 给我的吗？这个礼物很不错！$h#$b#You know, on a physiological level, I wouldn't advise the consumption of alcohol... / 呃，从生理学的角度来讲，我不是很建议喝酒……#$b#But there's no denying the benefit of kicking back and enjoying a glass of fine Stardew Valley wine!$h / 不过不可否认，偶尔放松一下小酌一杯，还是有好处的！$h",
        "eventSeen_571102_memory": "I've never told anyone about my airplane hobby before... I guess I just feel comfortable talking to you. / 我之前从来没跟别人说过我对飞机感兴趣……不过跟你说的时候还是挺轻松的。",
        "summer_Mon": "It's okay to get a moderate amount of sunlight. Just don't get burnt. / 适度晒晒太阳是有好处的。只要别晒伤就行。#$e#Okay. Take care! Stay healthy. / 好。多多保重！注意身体健康。",
        "Wed4": "I'd like to get to know you better, @. Let's put aside our doctor-patient relationship. / 我很愿意进一步了解你，@。我们先把医患关系抛到一边。",
        "eventSeen_56": "As a small town doctor, you can't help but form a personal connection with your patients. That can be both good and bad... / 作为小镇医生，总会不可避免地与病人建立起个人联系，这既有好处也有坏处……",
        "fall_Fri": "Have you been going into the mines, @? / 你去过矿井吗，@？#$e#It's a dangerous place. I recommend against it. / 那里很危险。最好别去。",
        "eventSeen_56_memory_twoweeks": "I tried making my own pickles one time...$s / 我尝试过自己做泡菜……$s#$e#Um, let me put it this way... The frogs we dissected in high school smelled like roses in comparison... / 呃，这么说吧……跟那个比起来，我们高中解剖的青蛙简直是沁人心脾……",
        "Sat": "Can I do anything for you? / 我能帮你什么？#$e#Take care. / 保重。",
        "Fri": "It's a beautiful day, isn't it? / 今天天气真好啊。#$e#I wish I had less work to do.$s / 希望工作能少点。$s",
        "Resort_Leaving": "If you get burnt, a little aloe vera cream might help soothe the skin. / 如果你晒伤了，抹一点芦荟胶应该能让皮肤感觉舒服些。",
        "Resort_Bar": "It's important to stay hydrated in this heat. I'm going to ask Gus if he has any coconut water!$h / 天气这么热，补水是很重要的。我要去问问格斯，看他有没有椰子水！$h",
        "event_george2": "*Sigh*$s / *唉*……$s#$b#Look, George. If you want to behave like this I'm going to have to tell your wife. I don't think she'll be happy. / 看，乔治。如果你一直这样我只能告诉你妻子了。她估计会发火吧。",
        "dumped_Guys": "I'm busy with my work. I can't speak to you.$s / 我忙于工作。无法和你说话。$s",
        "event_george1": "Thanks, @.$h / 谢谢你，@。$h#$b#You see, George, I'm just trying to help you. / 乔治，我只是在帮你。"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/Jas",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "eventSeen_3910975": "...Is Shane going to be okay?$s / ……谢恩没事吧？$s",
        "GreenRain_2": "I hope the rain doesn't turn my dress green...$s / 希望雨水不要把我的裙子变成绿色……$s",
        "eventSeen_3910974": "*giggle* ...look, I've got real bunny-jewel slippers!$h / 嘻嘻……快看，我有正版的兔子宝石拖鞋啦！$h",
        "Sun10": "Did you know Shane's my godfather? He was a friend of my parents.$s / 你知道吗？谢恩是我的教父。他是我父母的朋友。$s#$e#...they died. *sniff*$s / ……他们都去世了。*啜泣*$s",
        "Resort_Entering": "I see a crab! / 我看到螃蟹了！",
        "Resort": "Aunt Marnie told me not to get burnt... But when I walk fast, it feels cool, so I think I'll be okay.$h / 玛妮姑妈叮嘱我别晒伤了……但如果我走得够快，就会感觉很凉爽，所以应该没事的。$h",
        "Thu2": "Miss Penny is teaching me how to write in cursive.$h / 潘妮小姐在教我连笔字。$h#$e#She has such pretty handwriting. / 她的书法真好。",
        "Thu": "I'm not supposed to talk to strangers...$u / 我不该和陌生人说话……$u",
        "Sat8": "You're always so nice to me, ${Mr.^Ms.}$ @.$h / 你总是这么好， @${先生^女士}$$h#$e#Grown-ups are usually mean and boring, but you're different. / 大人们总是刻薄又无聊，但是你不会。",
        "Introduction": "...$u / ……$u#$b#Hi...$u / 你好……$u",
        "reject_869": "Ew, gross!$s / 哎呀，恶心！$s",
        "Mon": "Oh...Are you looking for Aunt Marnie?$u / 哦……你是在找玛妮姑妈吗？$u",
        "movieTheater": "Aunt Marnie says I'm not old enough to see a movie by myself...$s / 玛妮阿姨说我还太小，不能一个人看电影……$s",
        "Tue6": "You can play with my dolls if you want to. Just make sure to brush their hair when you're done. / 想玩我的娃娃的话不用客气。但是玩完别忘了给她们梳头发。",
        "Wed2": "...Hi.$u / ……嗨。$u",
        "AcceptGift_Negative_alcohol_item": "Umm... I'm not supposed to drink this. Isn't it for adults?$s / 呃……这个不是大人喝的吗？我还不能喝。$s",
        "Sun": "Um... d...do you want something?$u / 嗯……你……你想要点什么？$u#$e#I'm not supposed to talk to strangers.$u / 我不该和陌生人说话。$u",
        "Fri2": "Do you like my bow? / 你喜欢我的蝴蝶结吗？",
        "Wed": "...$u / ……$u",
        "AcceptGift_(O)103": "Oh, a little dolly! She's kind of dirty, but I'll give her a bath. Thanks!$h / 啊，是个娃娃！有点脏嘛，我要给它洗个澡。谢谢你！$h",
        "AcceptBirthdayGift_Positive": "Wow, a birthday present! I love it!$h / 哇，是生日礼物！我很喜欢！$h",
        "married": "*sigh*... I hope I can get married some day.$u / 唉……希望有朝一日我也能结婚。$u",
        "Fri4": "I like living on the farm... my favorite is the fresh ice cream from our cows' milk. / 我喜欢住在农场……用自家产牛奶做出来的新鲜牛奶冰淇淋是我的最爱！",
        "GreenRain": "I'm scared...$s / 我好害怕……$s",
        "cropMatured_595": "$y 'Um... Have you ever seen a fairy?_Yes_Wow! I wanna see one, too.$h_No_...Me neither.$s' / $y '呃……你见过仙子吗？_见过_哇！我也想看看。$h_没见过_……我也没有。$s'",
        "Tue": "What? *giggle*$h / 什么？* 咯咯笑 *$h#$e#...hi. / ……嗨。",
        "AcceptBirthdayGift_Negative": "A birthday present? Oh... I don't like this.$s / 是生日礼物吗？啊……我不喜欢。$s",
        "AcceptGift_(O)StardropTea": "Are you sure? It smells so good! I'll only drink a thimbleful a day.$h / 确定要给我吗？好香啊！那我每天喝一丁点。$h",
        "Sun2": "Shane's gone a lot, and Aunt Marnie is busy all the time... so I have to invent my own games. / 谢恩经常不在，玛妮姑妈又很忙……所以我得自己发明游戏。#$e#I'm thankful for all my toys.$h / 感谢我的玩具们。$h",
        "Sat2": "Sometimes I look for crawdads in the river. Don't tell Aunt Marnie... but I fed one to a cow once. / 我有时会去河里捉小龙虾。别告诉玛妮姑妈……但是我有一次喂一头牛吃了一只。#$e#She loved it. / 她可喜欢了。",
        "Resort_Shore": "I'm collecting seashells... I'm gonna make a necklace! / 我在收集贝壳……我要做一条项链！",
        "Mon4": "Hi, Mr. @. / 嗨，@先生。^Hi, Ms. @. / 嗨，@女士。#$e#It's fun to live on a farm.$h / 农场生活是很有趣的哦。$h",
        "married_Shane": "I hope Shane will still come and see me...$s / 我希望谢恩还会过来陪我……$s",
        "AcceptGift_Negative_coffee_item": "Oh... Aunt Marnie doesn't let me drink coffee yet...$s / 啊……玛妮阿姨还不让我喝咖啡……$s",
        "eventSeen_3910975_memory_oneweek": "I had a nightmare that the house was on fire...$s / 我做了个噩梦，梦见家里着火了……$s",
        "Wed4": "Aunt Marnie won't let me go out after 6 o'clock. It's not fair!$s / 玛妮姑妈 6 点之后不让我出门了。这不公平！$s#$e#I'm not afraid of the dark anymore! / 我早就不怕黑了！",
        "AcceptGift_(TR)FairyBox": "Wow, it's so pretty! And there's a fairy inside? *giggle*... I can hear her singing. She'll be my secret friend.$h / 哇，好漂亮！里面还有仙女？哈哈……我听到她在唱歌了，我要偷偷跟她做好朋友。$h",
        "Sat": "You smell like grass.$u / 你身上有青草的味道。$u",
        "AcceptGift_Positive_doll_item": "Oh, I like him! He'll fit right in with my other friends.$h / 啊，这个好好玩！跟我的朋友们放在一起肯定很合适。$h",
        "Fri": "... I don't know you.$u / ……我不认识你。$u",
        "Resort_Leaving": "I've got sand in my shoe...$s / 我鞋里进沙子了……$s"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/Jodi",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "eventSeen_3910975": "*whisper* Did you hear about Shane? That's so terrible... I hope he's doing okay.$s / （低声说）你听说谢恩的事了吗？太惨了……希望他能缓过来。$s",
        "fall_Thu": "Maybe I've spoiled the boys a bit. They've never had to do any chores. / 也许是我有点宠坏孩子了。他们从来不干活。#$e#I guess I want them to be able to enjoy their childhood while they still can. Well, Sam's basically a man now, though. / 我是想在他们小的时候给他们一个好的童年。不管怎样，山姆现在长大成人了。#$b#I hope he hasn't grown up to be lazy. That won't do.$s / 希望他不要变得懒惰。太懒惰可不行。$s#$e#Being a parent isn't very easy. / 做父母真不容易啊。",
        "GreenRain_2": "Vincent got up early to go play in the rain. I just hope they're right about it being completely harmless! / 文森特一大早就跑到雨里玩去了，但愿他们说这场雨完全无害是真的！",
        "Mon6": "It's nice to have a family... but I'd be lying if I said I never miss the freedom of being young...$s / 有个家确实挺好的……但是如果我说我从不渴望年轻时的自由肯定是在撒谎……$s",
        "Resort": "The view is breathtaking! Deep blue as far as the eye can see... / 这景色真是摄人心魄！极目远眺，都是一片深蓝……",
        "Resort_Entering": "What a treat! / 多么享受啊！",
        "Thu": "So you're a farmer, huh? Interesting. / 你是位农夫，是吧？有意思。#$e#I've never met a farmer before. / 我第一次认识农夫。#$e#Maybe some day you can teach me how to grow vegetables.$h / 也许以后你可以教我怎么种菜。$h",
        "summer_Thu": "Housework is frustrating because you're never finished. / 家务很令人烦躁，因为你永远干不完。#$e#The day after I sweep the floor, it's dirty again. / 拖完地的第二天，又脏了。",
        "Thu6": "Where does all the time go? *sigh* / 时间都去哪了？*唉*#$e#I remember when Sam was a little baby wearing diapers. He was such a cute little kid.$s / 我还记得山姆小时候穿尿布的样子呢。他那时多可爱。$s#$e#Don't tell him I said that.$h / 你可别告诉他我说过这话。$h#$e#You must really like talking to me, huh? / 你一定很爱跟我聊天吧？",
        "dating_Sam_memory_oneday": "I heard about you and Sam. Hopefully he won't cause you any trouble!$h / 我听说你跟山姆在一起了，但愿他不会给你惹麻烦！$h",
        "Introduction": "Oh! You aren't exactly how I imagined... but that's okay! I'm Jodi. / 噢！你和我想象中的有点不一样呢……但是没关系！我是乔迪。#$e#It's a quiet little town, so it's very exciting when someone new moves in! Having a farmer around could really change things. / 这是个宁静的小镇，所以能有人搬进来真的让人高兴呢！有个农场主确实可以改变很多事。",
        "Mon": "Maintaining a household is difficult work... but somebody has to do it. / 维持一个家庭是很不容易的事……但是总得有人做吧。#$e#Yes? / 怎么了？",
        "fall_Thu_inlaw_Sam": "Is Sam just bumming around the farm, or is he contributing? / 山姆只是在农场闲逛，还是在帮着做事？",
        "winter_Tue6": "*sigh*... Sometimes I dream about life on my own... without a family to look after. Is that horrible?$s / *唉* ……有时候我会梦到自己孤身一人……没有一个需要照顾的家。这听起来很恐怖吗？$s#$e#Don't tell anyone.$4 / 不要告诉任何人哦。$4",
        "winter_Tue": "Hi. Do you get tired of people asking about your farm all the time? / 嗨。人们总是问你农场的事情，你会不会觉得烦？#$e#I think I would. / 要是我的话我肯定会。",
        "reject_864": "What's this? It looks like one of Kent's buddies from the war. Maybe you should show it to him? / 这是什么？看起来像是肯特的一位战友。也许你应该把这个拿去给他看看？",
        "cc_Bus": "They say the bus is back up and running. I'm sure Pam is happy about that... / 她们说巴士修好了可以开了，潘姆肯定很高兴。#$b#I heard she'd been drinking more after losing her job... so hopefully this helps. / 我听说她失业之后喝得更凶了……希望能有所好转吧。",
        "Sun": "#$c .5#I'm taking a break from house chores today.$h / #$c .5#今天不做家务活了，我要休息一下。$h#$e#I'm taking the day off.$h / 我今天休息。$h#$e#If I don't spend any time outside, I'll go crazy! / 我再不出去待会我就要疯了！#$e#Plus I don't want my legs to turn soft. / 再说，我也不想骨头生锈。",
        "Wed": "What did you say? It's %time already? My goodness! / 你说什么？都已经 %time 了？天哪！#$e#I still have tons of work to do!$s / 我还有成堆的工作没做呢！$s",
        "fall_Sun2": "When you become a parent, you have to leave your old lifestyle behind. / 等你成了家长，你就得放下你过去的生活方式。#$e#Maybe that's not entirely true... but if you're not careful, it will happen. / 可能倒也不绝对……不过这种事总是在你不经意间就悄悄发生了。",
        "summer_Tue_inlaw_Sam": "How's my little Sammy doing on the old farm?$h / 我的小萨米在旧农场里干得怎么样？$h",
        "pamHouseUpgrade": "Wow... I heard what you did for Pam... Boy, I wonder what she did to get in your good graces like that?$s / 欸……我听说你帮了潘姆……好家伙，她干了什么让你对她这么好？$s#$e#...I wish I had that kind of money to throw around...$s / ……要是我也有这么多钱可以挥霍就好了……$s",
        "winter_Wed4_2": "Kent has been home for a while now, but he still seems uneasy.$s / 肯特已经在家呆了一段时间了，但他还是一副心神不宁的样子。$s",
        "Sun8": "I had a dream that I had complete freedom, no obligation to anyone but myself... / 我梦到我彻底自由了，除了自己以外，对任何人都没有义务……#$b#...Then I woke up and realized I had a full day of house chores ahead of me...$s / …………然后我梦醒了并意识到我眼前有一堆家务活儿……$s#$e#But I don't regret having a family, @... Sam and Vincent mean everything to me! / 但我不后悔有一个家庭，@……山姆和文森对我来说意味着一切！",
        "winter_Fri": "It would be nice to take a vacation once in a while...$s / 感觉偶尔休休假也会挺不错的……$s",
        "winter_Sun": "If I was rich the first thing I'd do would be to hire a maid and a chef. / 如果我有钱了，我要做的第一件事就是雇一名女仆和一名厨师。#$e#My goodness, that would be nice!$h / 我的天啊，想想就很美！$h",
        "GreenRain": "Are you alright? We've never seen anything like this before...$s / 你没事吗？我们以前从来没见过这种情况……$s#$e#I wish my husband was here. He'd know exactly what to do.$s / 要是我老公在就好了，他肯定知道该怎么办。$s",
        "eventSeen_3102768": "Penny's a sweet girl. She's been Vincent's teacher for a while now, and he really loves her. / 潘妮是个温柔的孩子。她当文森特的老师有一段时间了，文森特很喜欢她。",
        "winter_Thu_inlaw_Sam": "How's Sam doing? I have to admit, there's less cooking and cleaning to do since he moved out... / 山姆怎么样？我必须承认，自从他搬出去后很少需要做饭和打扫了……",
        "Tue": "Exercise is important for staying healthy. I always make sure to set aside some time for it. / 想保持健康的话，锻炼必不可少。我总是抽时间锻炼。#$e#As a parent, I don't have much time to devote to myself. So I try and make every minute count. / 作为家长，我没什么时间可以花在自己身上。因此我尽可能的抓紧每分每秒。",
        "AcceptGift_(O)StardropTea": "Ah... You sure you want to give away such a precious item? Well, thank you! / 啊……你确定要送这么珍贵的东西吗？好吧，谢谢你！",
        "summer_Tue": "Hello. / 你好。#$e#Do you need something? I'm a little busy. / 你需要什么？我有点忙。",
        "fall_Mon6": "I should count my blessings more often. We have a good life here. Some people don't have enough food to eat.$s / 我应该多珍惜福气的，毕竟我们已经过得很好了，有些人还是缺衣少食。$s",
        "eventSeen_101": "Poor Clint... they say he's head-over-heels for Emily, but I've heard she only thinks of him as a friend... / 克林特太惨了……她们说他对艾米丽那是爱惨了，但我听说艾米丽只把他当朋友……",
        "winter_Thu8": "We kind of rushed into our marriage, with Kent being a soldier and all... I hardly got a taste of youth and freedom, and now it's too late to ever go back.$s / 因为肯特是军人，以及其他种种原因，我们有点像是闪婚……我几乎没有感受过青春和自由，现在已经回不去了。$s#$e#I can't believe I'm saying this to you.$4 / 我不敢相信对你说了这些。$4",
        "Mon2": "$d kent#Yesterday I visited Yoba's Altar to give thanks for my husband's safe return. / 昨天我去了由巴祭坛感谢我丈夫能平安归来。|Yesterday I visited Yoba's Altar to ask for my husband's safe return. / 昨天我去了由巴祭坛祈求我丈夫能平安归来。#$e#I'm trying to stay positive, but it's hard sometimes. / 我也想保持乐观，但是有时感觉太难了。$s",
        "Sat4": "I'm so glad you're trying to improve that old farm. / 你能动手去翻新那座破旧的农场真是太好了。#$e#Once you've got everything in order, it's going to add a lot to our community!$h / 等你弄得差不多了，我们大家也都能跟着受益呢！$h#$e#It's going to be a lot of work for you, though. / 当然，也可是个大工程。#$e#Bye. / 再见。",
        "summer_Mon": "Summer is nice, but it also means more work. / 夏天很不错，但也有很多活。#$e#I'll have to keep the garden in shape on top of working in the house! / 我得修剪花园接着还得做家务！",
        "Wed4": "I wish I could spend more time outside, but there's so much work to do. / 我真希望能多到外面转转，但是有太多的活要干了。#$e#I started wearing rubber gloves to keep my hands soft. / 我戴上橡胶手套保护手。#$e#The older you get, the more work you have to do to stay healthy.$s / 年纪越大，越得花更多精力保持健康。$s#$e#Ok, bye! / 好，再见！",
        "winter_Wed2": "What do I do for fun? Hmm... That's a good question. / 我是怎么找乐子的？嗯……这是个好问题。#$e#I like sleeping.$s / 我喜欢睡觉。$s",
        "eventSeen_58": "I've been doing aerobics class with the ladies every week... / 我每周都跟她们一起上有氧健身课……#$b#Recently, someone new joined the class, but he made us all swear we wouldn't reveal his identity! / 最近来了个新人，不过他让我们发誓不能透露他的身份！",
        "summer_Sun": "What in the world am I going to make for dinner? / 晚饭到底做什么啊？#$e#*sigh*... / *唉* ……",
        "pamHouseUpgradeAnonymous": "Did you see Pam's new house? Boy... I wish I had that kind of money... I'd love to get the kitchen remodeled, at least...$s / 你看到潘姆的新房子了吗？好家伙……要是我也有这么多钱就好了……好歹能把厨房重新装修一下……$s",
        "Sat": "Hi. / 嗨。#$e#Need something? / 需要什么吗？",
        "fall_Sun": "Caroline and I are good friends. I tell her everything. / 我和卡洛琳是好朋友。我什么事情都跟她说。",
        "2_1": "My husband Kent is a soldier, working overseas. That's why he's not here right now. / 我丈夫肯特是位士兵，在海外服役。因此他现在不在。#$b#I know he'll come back safe once his tour is over!! / 他服役完了后一定会安全归来的！！！#$e#Need something? / 需要什么吗？",
        "winter_Mon": "I loved playing in the snow when I was a kid. The great thing about being a mother is that I get to enjoy it again.$h / 我小时候很喜欢玩雪。当妈妈最大的好处之一就是我能够重温儿时的回忆。$h",
        "winter_Thu": "Sam makes a lot of noise with that music of his. I hope it doesn't disturb the neighbors. / 山姆的音乐太吵了。我希望不会打扰到邻居们。",
        "Fri": "$d Joja#The food at JojaMart might not be the healthiest for my family, but with such low prices you'd be crazy to shop anywhere else! / Joja 超市的食物虽说可能不是特别健康，但是那么低的价格真是让人发疯|The food at Pierre's is so much fresher and healthier than anything I ever bought at JojaMart. I do miss those cheap Joja prices, though. / 皮埃尔商店的食物比 Joja 超市的更新鲜也更健康。但我确实怀念 Joja 超市的价格。",
        "Resort_Leaving": "I think I'll make seafood tonight.$h / 我今晚大概会做海鲜。$h",
        "eventSeen_94": "Thanks again for bringing that fish! It was some of the best we've had in a while. / 上次你带来的那条鱼，真的很感谢！那是我们最近尝到的最美味的鱼了。",
        "Resort_Bar": "We all love it when Gus shows up. / 格斯在，我们就很开心。",
        "married_Sam": "I'm so happy for you and Sam. I think you two are the perfect match! / 你跟山姆结婚了我很开心，我觉得你们俩特别般配！#$e#I never thought I'd say it... but I'll miss those awful noises from Sam's guitar...$s / 没想到会有机会说出来……山姆弹的那些轰隆隆的噪音，我还是会想念的……$s"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/Kent",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "GreenRain_2": "Heh... The rain is a blessing. A reminder that there will always be forces greater than anything conceived of by man. / 哎呀……下这场雨是一件好事，能提醒我们山外有山，天外有天。#$e#That's actually a comfort, @. / @啊，这反而能让人放心下来。",
        "Tue2": "Things haven't changed much since I've been gone. / 我离开了之后，这里好像也没什么变化。#$e#Except that we have a new farmer in town.$h / 只不过镇子里多了一个新的农夫啦。$h",
        "Resort_Entering": "Hey, @. Nice to see you. / 嗨，@。见到你真好。",
        "Resort": "The boat ride was fun. I even got to use some of my nautical training to help navigate.$h / 这段航程挺有趣的，在导航的时候，我所接受的航海训练居然派上了一点用场。$h",
        "Thu": "Are you friends with my son? / 你们是我儿子的朋友吗？#$e#You probably know him better than I do...$s / 你们大概比我还了解他……$s",
        "Tue": "Things haven't changed much since I've been gone. / 我离开了之后，这里好像也没什么变化。#$e#Well, except that you're here. / 好吧，只不过多了个你。",
        "AcceptGift_(O)StardropTea": "For me? Well, that's unexpected... But I won't say no. Thanks! / 这是送我的吗？呃，有点意外……不过给我吧，谢谢你！",
        "Sat8": "I have trouble sleeping, so please excuse me if I seem tired. / 我有失眠的毛病，所以如果我看起来很疲惫的话，请你不要介意。#$e#I'm sure you can understand. / 我知道你可以理解的。",
        "Thu6": "#$1 Kent1#I've been up since 4 o'clock... sometimes I wonder if I'll ever get back into a normal routine. / 我 4 点钟就起来了……有时候我会怀疑自己能不能回到正常的生活作息上来。$k#$e#Sam has really grown up since I left. He's a man now. / 在我离开之后，山姆真的长大了。他现在是个真正的男人了。#$e#I wish I could've been there for him.$s / 我真希望能一直陪着他。$s",
        "event_popcorn1": "You keep quiet! Stop trying to turn me against my wife.$u / 别再说了！不要让我们夫妻俩发生矛盾了。$u",
        "event_popcorn2": "...$s / ……$s#$b#You're absolutely right, @.$s / 你说的完全正确，@。$s",
        "Mon": "Hello, farmer. / 你好啊。#$e#I've been gone so long... I feel like a stranger. / 我离开好久了啊……觉得自己就是个异乡客。",
        "accept_864": "...!$4 / ……！$4#$b#...Where did you find this?$4 / ……你是在哪找到这个的？$4#$b#...$5 / ……$5#$b#This man... We fought together in the war, @. He was like a brother to me.  / ……这个人……我们曾在战争中并肩作战，@。对我来说，他就像是兄弟一样。#$b#But... only one of us made it back.$5 / 可是……只有我活着回来了。$5#$b#He never lost his courage, though. Even in the face of death. A true hero... I'll never forget him. / 尽管如此，他从未丧失过勇气，即便面临死亡也是如此。他是真正的英雄……我永远不会忘记他。#$b#Thanks for bringing me this... It means a lot to me. / 谢谢你把这个带给我……这对我来说很重要。#$b#Here, take this. It's been sitting in the back of our cupboard for years, and we've never used it. / 来，拿着这个。这东西放在我家橱柜深处已经很多年了，我们从来没用过。",
        "reject_865": "Yep... It's been tightly sealed, so the flavor should still be really potent. / 嗯……封得很紧，这样一来味道应该还是很足的。",
        "Tue6": "I feel like I'm settling back in pretty well. It's nice to have a friend in town.$h / 我觉得我适应得挺好的，有朋友在镇上我很开心。$h",
        "event_popcorn3": "Don't lie to me! I hate lies more than anything!$u / 别在我面前撒谎！我最讨厌的就是撒谎！$u",
        "MovieInvitation": "Erm... okay. Thank you. I'll meet you there.$h / 嗯……好的。谢谢。我们到时候见。$h",
        "Resort_Shore": "Standing on this beach... I feel a rare sense of peace.$h / 站在这片沙滩上……我感受到难得的平静。$h#$e#The ocean is a very special thing. / 这片海相当特别。",
        "Mon4": "I don't know if I'll ever get used to being back home. / 我不知道我还能不能适应家里的生活。#$e#The peacefulness of the town feels like a mask. That's probably just me though. / 镇子里的平静祥和像是一种掩饰。可能只有我觉得这样吧。",
        "Sun": "I don't know what to do with myself now that I'm back. / 虽然我回来了，但是我却不知道自己该做些什么。#$e#I'm used to having more structure in my day. / 我已经习惯了更有组织，有纪律的生活了。",
        "Wed": "You've been here a while now, haven't you? Your farm must be thriving. / 你已经在这儿呆了一段时间了，不是吗？你的农场现在一定是蒸蒸日上。",
        "Thu_inlaw_Sam": "Hey, @. Are you enjoying the married lifestyle? / 嘿，@。结婚了开心吗？",
        "Wed6": "...I lost a lot of friends in battle.$s / ……我在战争中失去了好多朋友。$s#$e#What's sad is that I can't even remember their faces. / 最可悲的是我居然连他们的面孔都想不起来了。#$e#... / ……",
        "Wed10": "To be alive is a special gift, and it comes and goes in the blink of an eye... never lose sight of that. / 生命本身就是特别的礼物，它说来就来，说走就走……永远不要忘记这一点。",
        "Sat": "Jodi tells me you've really become a part of this community. I'm glad to hear it. / 乔迪跟我说你已经完全融入到这个集体当中了。我很高兴。",
        "Sun4": "You've got a routine to keep you busy, huh? That's a good thing. / 你有一套固定的劳作流程是吧？那挺好的。#$e#Too much freedom can be stifling. We all benefit from having some structure in our lives. / 太自由了反而会很压抑，每天按部就班是有好处的。",
        "Resort_Chair": "This is a great place to bond with the family. I really appreciate you fixing it up. / 这个地方非常适合家庭成员加深感情。我真的很高兴你把这里修好了。",
        "Fri": "It looks like a decent day for fishing, doesn't it? / 今天真是个钓鱼的好日子，不是吗？",
        "eventSeen_100_memory_oneday": "My apologies for the other day. / 那天的事情非常抱歉。#$e#I don't want any special treatment. I just want to be a normal person, like everyone else. / 我不想被特殊对待，我只是想当一个普通人，跟大家一样。",
        "Resort_Leaving": "Time to head home. / 是时候回家了。",
        "Resort_Bar": "Just getting some water. / 来点水就好。",
        "Fri4": "I oughta take up fishing. It would give me something to do, keep my hands busy. / 我得学学钓鱼了，这样能有事可做，不至于闲着。",
        "married_Sam": "It makes a father proud to see his boy become a man. You have my heartfelt blessing.$h / 能看到儿子成长为一个男人，作为父亲我很自豪。希望你们以后能越过越好。$h",
        "AcceptGift_(O)Book_Bombs": "Well, I can't read Dwarvish, but it's an interesting collector's item. Thank you. / 哎，我看不懂矮人语，不过拿来收藏也挺有意思，谢谢你。"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/Krobus",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "Mon6": "'Krobus' means 'bridge-crosser' in our language. / 在我们的语言里，“科罗布斯”意思就是“过桥人”。",
        "GreenRain": "The flow of water has been unusually strong today... what's going on up there? / 今天水的流速特别快……地上发生什么了？",
        "8_*": "A 1000 year war between my people and the dwarves recently ended. There's still a lot of resentment on both sides. / 我们和矮人之间的千年战争最近终于结束了。不过彼此之间依然互相憎恨。",
        "AcceptGift_(O)Book_Void": "Hey, look! All my friends are in here!$h / 哎，快看！我朋友在这里都有！$h#$b#Wait a minute, is that me...?$7 / 等等，这是我吗……？$7",
        "AcceptGift_(O)308": "This smells delicious! I'll eat half, and use the other half to moisturize my body...$h / 好香啊！这样吧，一半我用来吃，另一半我用来涂保湿……$h",
        "AcceptBirthdayGift_Negative": "Oh... is this what you call a 'birthday present'? I don't understand humans...$s / 啊……你们说的“生日礼物”就是这种东西吗？我不是很懂人类……$s",
        "AcceptGift_(O)StardropTea": "Is that Stardrop Tea? Thank you! One drop makes my room smell good for the whole day. / 这是星之果茶吗？谢谢你！只要滴上一滴，我的屋子就能香上一整天。",
        "Thu": "Please don't tell anyone about me. / 请不要跟别人说关于我的事情。#$b#Humans tend to destroy things they can't understand. / 人类遇到自己不理解的事的时候似乎总喜欢一毁了之。",
        "Tue": "I am too sensitive to sunlight to go out on most days. / 我对阳光过敏，白天不敢出门。#$b#The conditions in here are perfect. / 这里的条件最理想了。#$e#Care to buy anything? / 想不想买点什么？",
        "Sat8": "I'll never know what it's like to be human... but talking to you, I feel like I understand it a little. / 我永远不会明白作为人类是什么感受……不过跟你聊天之后，我多少理解了一点。",
        "Thu6": "Please don't tell anyone about me. / 请不要把我的事情告诉别人。#$b#Most humans are frightened by us shadow people... maybe for good reason.$s / 大多数人类都很怕我们这些暗影人……可能有什么原因吧。$s#$b#But regardless, if the townspeople knew about me, I might not be safe here. / 但是，无论如何，如果镇民知道我的存在，我在这里就不安全了。",
        "Mon": "Please, don't be alarmed. I am different than the others. / 请你不要吃惊。我和别人不大一样。#$e#I've spent a lot of time observing humans. I know you like to shop. Care to see my wares? / 我花了很多时间观察研究人类。我知道你想要买东西。想要看看我都有些什么吗？",
        "eventSeen_691039": "...I'm a little bruised, but I'm okay. / ……我有点擦伤，不过没事。",
        "4_*": "...Have you encountered others like me, in the mines? I'm sorry if they were hostile towards you. You see, we've learned to fear humans... there have been too many... unpleasant encounters. / ……你有没有在矿井里面遇到其他像我这样的家伙？如果他们不太友好，我向你道歉。我们已经学会畏惧人类了……毕竟……有太多不愉快的遭遇。#$e#You haven't... slain any of my friends, have you? / 你……没有杀过我的朋友吧？",
        "Mon2": "Back again? I suppose it does fit into my theory of human behavior. / 你又来了？这确实很符合我的人类行为学理论。",
        "reject_868": "Oh, it's an arctic shard! That's a very rare magical item. / 哦，是极寒碎片！是非常罕见的魔法物品。#$b#I'd bring that to the Wizard if I were you! / 我觉得你应该把它拿去给法师看看！",
        "Sat4": "I'd love to see more of the outside world, but it wouldn't be safe for me.$s / 我很想去外面的世界看看，但对我不是很安全。$s",
        "Sun": "...Sorry, I'm still a little wary of humans. My shop is still open to you, however. / 抱歉……我还是有点不大习惯跟人类相处。但是我的商店依然会对你开放。",
        "15_*": "Please keep my location a secret. If the dwarves knew of me, they'd surely send an assassin. / 请不要向别人泄露我的位置。如果矮人知道了，他们肯定会派杀手来的。",
        "Wed": "I find things here and I sell them. Care to buy anything? / 我在这里搜寻值钱的东西，然后把它们卖掉。想不想买点什么？",
        "SpouseStardrop": "I wanted to give you this as a 'thank you' for letting me live here with you.$h / 我想送你这个，作为你允许我和你一起住的谢礼。$h",
        "Wed6": "If you put your ear up to the right pipe, you can hear into any house from down here. / 如果你把耳朵凑到正确的管子上，就可以从这里到任何房子的声音了。#$b#I wouldn't eavesdrop, though!$3 / 不过我不会偷听的！$3",
        "divorced": "... / ……",
        "Sat": "On Fridays I stay silent as a sign of devotion to Yoba. / 星期五的时候我会保持安静，以表示对由巴虔诚。",
        "18_*": "I try not to make too much noise down here. Imagine if the townspeople heard my weird sounds coming from the sewer drain... / 我待在这里会尽量保持安静的。假如镇上的人听到下水道里传来我奇怪的声音……",
        "Sun4": "You're not like the other humans, are you? / 你跟其他人不一样，对吗？",
        "AcceptBirthdayGift_Positive": "Oh, a gift to remember the day that I hatched! Thank you!$h / 哇，这是我孵化日的纪念礼物吗！谢谢你！$h",
        "Fri": "... / ……",
        "AcceptGift_(O)879": "A gift of lovely perfume? Oh, @... I'm blushing, but you probably can't notice...$4 / 这瓶好闻的香水是要送给我吗？哎呀，@……我都脸红了，不过你可能看不出来……$4",
        "Sun8": "You've opened my eyes to the world of humans. I appreciate that. / 你让我见识了人类的世界。非常感谢。"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/Leah",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "summer_Tue4": "The simple things in life are best: a soft summer breeze, majestic clouds, and a goblet full of Stardew Valley red. / 生活中简单的东西最棒了：夏天里一阵柔和的清风，宏伟的云，或者是一个装满了星露谷红酒的酒杯。",
        "winter_Fri6": "Do you ever get cold in that farmhouse of yours? / 你有没有在你的农舍里挨过冻？#$e#Stop by my cabin if you want to huddle under one of my quilts and drink cider.$h / 如果你想要窝在我的被子里喝点苹果酒的话，就来我的小屋里坐坐吧。$h",
        "Fri8": "Do you ever wonder what it's like to be a different person? / 你有没有想过，假如变成另一个人会是什么感觉？#$e#Do our thoughts manifest in a similar way, or is it radically different? / 我们的思想是表现出类似的模式，还是截然不同？#$e#Don't mind me, I think about weird things sometimes...$h / 不用管我，我偶尔会想一些奇奇怪怪的事情……$h",
        "Resort_Entering": "Don't tell anyone, but Willy let me steer the boat for a few minutes.$h / 别告诉其他人哦，威利允许我开几分钟的船。$h",
        "Thu": "There's actually a lot of wild food in this area, if you know where to look. / 这附近其实有很多野生的食物，只要你知道去哪儿找就行。#$e#I've been having fresh salads almost every day.$h / 我几乎每天都吃新鲜的沙拉。$h",
        "Sat8": "$query PLAYER_NPC_RELATIONSHIP current any married roommate#I've thought about growing some crops, but I think I'd feel bad having to clear out all the wild plants to make space.|Farming sounds so fun. I want to try it, someday.$l / $query PLAYER_NPC_RELATIONSHIP current any married roommate#我有考虑过种点东西，但为了腾出地方就要除掉野草我会有罪恶感的。|种田听起来好有趣啊。我以后也想试试。$l",
        "Thu6": "Foraging is a specialty of mine. Someday I'll make you a fresh salad.$h / 我的特长之一就是采集。我以后也会为你做一顿新鲜的沙拉的。$h",
        "fall_1": "How quickly the seasons change! / 季节转换得好快啊！#$e#It's shocking. / 真是令人吃惊。",
        "fall_Tue": "I wonder if I could make a collage out of dried leaves? / 我想知道我能不能用干的落叶做一副拼贴画。#$e#They're just so colorful... I can't help but think of the potential for art projects.$h / 这些叶子的颜色太丰富了……我不禁就会去想艺术创作的潜力。$h",
        "Introduction": "Hello, it's nice to meet you. $h / 你好，很高兴见到你。$h#$e#You picked a good time to move here... The spring is lovely. / 你搬过来的时机选得挺好嘛……这里的春天非常迷人。",
        "event_parents5": "*sigh*...$s / *唉*……$s#$b#Maybe you're right... Humans are selfish creatures. I don't know. $s / 或许你是对的……人类是自私的生物。我不知道。$s#$b#I probably shouldn't dwell on it. We all have to make hard choices from time to time.$s / 我也许不该去细想。有的时候，我们都得做出一些艰难的决定。$s",
        "event_parents4": "*sigh*...$s / *唉*……$s#$b#I guess you're right... it was kind of selfish. But can you really blame me for wanting to be happy? Ugh... I don't know...$s / 我想你是对的……这样的确有点自私。但是你真的能因为我想要追求幸福就责备我吗？呃……我不知道……$s",
        "summer_Sat": "The flowing water keeps my house a little bit cooler in summer. / 水流能让我的小屋子夏天的时候能够稍微凉快一些。#$e#I can't tolerate heat very well. / 我不是很能忍受炎热。",
        "Mon": "The trees look nice today, don't they?#$q 21/22/211132 Mon_old#So why did you become a farmer?#$r 21 -5 Mon_21#I want to make tons of money.#$r 22 5 Mon_22#It's more \"real\" than living in the city.#$r 211132 5 Mon_211132#To follow in Grandpa's footsteps.#$r 22 5 Mon_22#I wanted to escape my old life. / 这些树今天看起来真美，不是吗？#$q 21/22/211132 Mon_old#所以你为什么要做一个农夫呢？#$r 21 -5 Mon_21#我想要赚很多很多的钱。#$r 22 5 Mon_22#住在这里比住在城市里要更“真实”。#$r 211132 5 Mon_211132#为了追随爷爷的脚步。#$r 22 5 Mon_22#我想要逃离我原来的生活。",
        "secondChance_Girls": "You caused a lot of grief with what you did... but I'm ready to put the past behind us.$s / 你所做的事情令人很伤心……但是我已经准备好不计前嫌。$s",
        "summer_1": "You can tell it's summer by the sweet smell of nectar wafting through the air!$h / 你能从空气中飘荡着的花蜜香味中感受到夏天的气息！$h",
        "Resort_Wander_2": "I wonder what kind of things you could forage out here. / 不知道你在这里能采集到什么样的东西。#$e#I think I saw some tasty looking walnuts growing on a bush nearby. / 我似乎在附近的灌木上见到了一些看起来很美味的核桃。",
        "FlowerDance_Decline": "I'll be honest. I don't want to dance with you.$u / 我就直说了。我不想跟你跳舞。$u",
        "event_sculpt3": "You pig!%fork$a / 你这头猪！%fork$a^Oh! You're...? Me too.$6 / 噢！你……？我也是。$6#$b#Get out!$a / 出去！$a^That's good to know.$l / 很高兴听你这么说。$l",
        "fall_Wed": "It's so nice to live by the river. / 住在河边真的太棒了。#$e#I fall asleep to the soothing sound of water every night. / 我每天都伴着轻柔的水流声入睡。",
        "Fri2": "We wouldn't be able to survive without nature. It's good to remember that. / 如果没有大自然，我们也不可能存活。知道这一点就让人感到很安心了。",
        "Wed": "#$1 LeahBug#This morning I accidentally stepped on a bug.$s / #$1 LeahBug#今天早上我一不小心踩到了一只虫子。$s#$e#Sometimes I think it's impossible to live without destroying nature in some way. / 有时候我觉得，某种程度上，活着而又不破坏大自然是件不可能的事情。",
        "dumped_Girls": "I don't want to see you for a while...$s / 在一段时间里，我不想见到你……$s",
        "fall_Sat": "Decorations accentuate the feeling of the season. I think it's a worthwhile tradition. / 装饰让四季的感觉更鲜明了。我觉得这个传统挺有意义的。",
        "AcceptBirthdayGift_Positive": "Hey, thanks a bunch, @! This makes my birthday feel special.$h / 哎，@，谢谢你！这个生日我过得很难忘。$h",
        "Resort_Chair": "I like the heat as long as I'm keeping perfectly still.$h / 我喜欢这样的热天气，只要我一动不动就很舒服。$h",
        "fall_Sun4": "One thing I love about this place is that there are beautiful waterfalls. / 这个地方吸引我的一个原因就是有很多漂亮的瀑布。#$e#Do you ever spend time watching them? It's soothing... / 你有没有停下来观赏过？让人有放松的感觉……",
        "AcceptGift_(O)196": "$c 0.8#This looks delicious... Thank you! There's nothing quite like a fresh, wild salad.$h#Oh, wow, @! This is exactly what I was craving! How'd you know?$h / $c 0.8#看起来好好吃……谢谢你！新鲜的沙拉最健康了。$h#哇，我正好想吃这个！@，你怎么知道的？$h",
        "Mon_211132": "That's very sweet to honor your grandfather like that. / 像这样纪念自己的爷爷真的很棒。",
        "winter_Fri": "Time seems to move slower here. / 在这里，时间好像过的更慢了。#$e#When I lived in the city, the year went by so fast. / 当我还住在城里的时候，一年年过得那可真快。",
        "summer_Fri6": "Hello, @. Do you ever get lonely on that big farm? / 你好啊，@。住在那个大农场会不会觉得孤单呢？#$e#Stop by my cabin if you ever need someone to talk to.$h / 如果你想找人聊天的话，就来我的小屋坐坐吧。$h",
        "event_sculpt2": "There's nothing wrong with that... I think there's lots of beauty to be found in raw, untouched nature! / 那并没有什么错……我觉得原始的、人迹罕至的大自然里有很多美好的东西。#$b#But as a human, I'm also interested in how we shape and interpret the world around us... I guess what I'm saying is that I'm interested in 'art'. / 但是作为一个人类，我也对我们如何塑造以及理解周围的世界这些事情感兴趣。因此我是想说我对“艺术”感兴趣。",
        "winter_Sun": "Do you ever take a whole day off? / 你有没有休息过一整天？#$e#It's a refreshing break. / 那样休息一天可真是让人精神振奋呢。",
        "GreenRain": "Where did all these plants come from? It's a surprise, but I'm not complaining... / 这些植物是从哪来的？有点惊喜，我觉得还挺好的……",
        "fall_Mon": "#$c .5#I found some wild mushrooms over the weekend! / #$c .5#我周末找到了一些野生蘑菇。#$e#I had a huge plate of wild mushrooms and eggs for breakfast today... I'm still full. / 我今天早上的时候吃了一大盘的野生蘑菇还有鸡蛋……我现在都还觉得很饱呢。#$e#Keep your nose to the ground and you'll find some mushrooms yourself... I'm sure of it. / 走路的时候低头找找，你也能找到蘑菇的……我很确定你可以。",
        "summer_Fri4": "Do you ever walk out into the forest... Pause... And simply enjoy the beauty of nature? / 你有没有试过走进森林……驻足……然后单纯地感受大自然的美好？#$e#It's easy to forget how incredible this world actually is... / 人们很容易会忘记这个世界有多么神奇……",
        "breakUp": "Ohh... Got it. Hah... I really don't have any luck when it comes to this stuff...$s / 哦……知道了。嗬……在这种事情上我真是倒霉极了。$s",
        "AcceptGift_(O)StardropTea": "Oh, wow... I had a sip of this stuff when I was a kid, and I've never forgotten the taste. / 哇……我小时候喝过一口这个，味道我到现在还记得。",
        "Tue4": "Hi. Oh, you want to talk? / 嗨。噢，你想聊聊是吗？#$e#The landscape around here gives me a lot of ideas. The terrain is almost like a sculpture itself. / 这附近的风景给我很多灵感。大地本身就如同一件雕塑。#$e#I don't make art for money. It's just an urge that I have. / 我创作不是为了钱。我的艺术创作完全是一种冲动。#$e#Farming seems like a very rewarding profession. You get to create delicious food for everyone!$h / 感觉种地是个好处很多的职业。你能为大家种出很多好吃的食物。$h#$e#You're probably busy. Sorry. / 你大概很忙吧。抱歉。",
        "summer_Tue": "The sound of farm animals is great, isn't it? / 农场里动物的叫声真是棒极了，对吧？",
        "winter_Sat": "Hello. Do you want something? / 你好。你在找什么东西吗？",
        "AcceptGift_(O)430": "Hey, where'd you find that? *sniff*... Mmm... This will be perfect, grated over a fresh pasta. Thank you!$h / 哎，这是在哪里找到的？（闻了一下）……嗯……磨碎了撒在意面上肯定很好吃，谢谢你！$h",
        "FlowerDance_Accept": "You want to dance with me? Yes!$h / 你想和我跳舞吗？好啊！$h#$e#I was wondering if you'd ask me...$h / 我一直在想你会不会邀请我……$h",
        "Resort_Shore": "The shape of the waves here is awe inspiring. / 这边海浪的形状真是令人惊叹。#$e#I wonder if I could ever capture that sort of formlessness in a sculpture. / 不知道我能不能通过雕塑将这种造型不定的感觉表现出来。",
        "AcceptGift_(O)169": "Oh! Thank you! This one has an interesting shape...$h / 啊！谢谢你！这根的形状有点奇特……$h",
        "event_parents2": "That's a little harsh... but, yeah. We had different priorities.$u / 虽然有点残酷……但是，没错。我们的价值观不一样。$u",
        "summer_Fri2": "I hate to be blunt, but if we don't treat nature with respect, our grandchildren will be doomed. / 我讨厌说话这么直白，但如果我们不对自然心怀敬畏的话，我们的子孙就没有未来。#$e#Don't you think so? / 你不这么觉得吗？",
        "summer_Sun": "What should I do on such a warm, lazy day? *sigh* / 在这个炎热又慵懒的日子里我该做什么呢？*唉*#$e#Any ideas? / 有什么建议吗？",
        "Wed6": "I love being around animals. They're so innocent. / 我喜欢和动物呆在一起。它们是如此的天真。#$e#Farm animals are wonderful, too.$h / 农场里的动物也很棒。$h",
        "Mon_22": "Hey... That's pretty much the reason I came here, too!$h#$b#I wanted to connect with nature more... / 我也是因为这个才来这里的！$h",
        "Beach": "I came for the sound of the ocean. Beautiful, isn't it? / 我是为了大海的声音而来的。充满诗意，不是吗？",
        "fall_Sun": "There's a lot of good places to walk around here. / 这附近有非常多地方很值得去走走。#$e#It feels good to stretch your legs. / 舒展舒展筋骨感觉很不错。",
        "winter_Thu": "I'm having a hard time finding fresh food to eat. / 我找不到新鲜的食物了。#$e#I've been eating a lot of bread.$s / 我最近吃了好多面包。$s",
        "fall_Tue4": "Everyone has a unique and interesting perspective, whether they believe it or not. Don't you think so? / 每个人都有独特而有趣的观点，不管他们信不信。你不这么觉得吗？#$e#Although, some people have opinions that I just can't respect. / 尽管一些人的观点我实在无法认同。",
        "GreenRain_2": "Imagine if this rain lasted all summer... The plants would take over the entire valley! / 假如这场雨下一整个夏天……星露谷里肯定会长满植物！",
        "winter_Wed": "I saw a snow rabbit early this morning! They're rare, aren't they? / 我今天早上看到雪兔了！它们可是非常稀有的呢。",
        "Resort": "I love the weather in Stardew Valley, but seeing a different climate now and then helps put things into perspective. / 我喜欢星露谷的天气，不过偶尔体验一下不同的气候也能让人耳目一新。",
        "Mon_21": "Hmm. That seems kind of shallow, doesn't it?$s / 嗯。听起来有点阴暗，不是吗？$s",
        "event_sculpt1": "...What?$7 / ……什么？$7#$b#Oh! Yeah, that's absolutely right!$h / 噢！是的，完全正确！$h",
        "winter_Sat2": "Hello, @. Is there something you wanted to talk about? / 你好啊，@。你有什么想要聊聊的吗？",
        "eventSeen_54_memory_oneday": "I'm still fuming about the picnic... what a weirdo!$a / 想起野餐的事情我就窝火……真是个怪人！$a#$b#Let's never talk about... that person... ever again.$s / 我们以后别再提起……那个人了。$s",
        "winter_Sun4": "You should take a whole day off, now and then. / 你应该每隔一阵子休息一两天。#$b#Not only is it good for the soul, but in the long run, you'll actually be more productive! / 不仅对精神有好处，而且长远来看，整体的干活效率其实会提高！",
        "Wed8": "$query PLAYER_NPC_RELATIONSHIP current any married roommate#It must be satisfying to harvest a whole field of crops, huh? You're basically creating food out of nothing!$h|Hi @! I was just thinking about you and your farm. / $query PLAYER_NPC_RELATIONSHIP current any married roommate#收获一整块地的庄稼肯定很有成就感吧？简直就像是凭空变出了饭菜一样！$h|嗨，@！我刚刚还在考虑你农场的事情呢。#$e#I was imagining how good it must feel to harvest a big bunch of crops.$h / 有这么大一块地，收获起来一定感觉不错吧。$h#$e#Wouldn't it be nice to have help, though?$l / 不过如果有人能帮你就好了。$l",
        "event_parents3": "Oh yeah? Well maybe I'll just leave, then!%fork$a / 是吗？那么也许我该走了！%fork$a",
        "winter_Tue": "It gets pretty cold in my little cabin.$s / 我的小屋里挺冷的。$s#$e#I just snuggle up under a huge blanket, and I'm okay.$h / 我一般会窝在大毯子下面，感觉很棒。$h",
        "eventSeen_53_memory_oneday": "I sold enough art at that show to get by for another year... that's all I needed! / 我在艺术展上赚到的钱够我再用一年了……有这些我就很满足了！",
        "GreenRainFinished": "I guess everyone in town was scared of that strange rain? I had no idea... I just thought it was incredible!$h / 镇上的大伙是不是都被奇怪的雨吓到了？我的话……我反而觉得这场雨太好了！$h",
        "summer_Sat4": "One Summer, it was so hot during the night that I got out of bed and jumped into the river! / 有一年夏天，晚上实在太热了，我只好爬起来出门扎进了河里！#$e#I hope no one saw me!$h / 但愿没人看见！$h",
        "Sun": "If you hear any banging from inside my hut, it's probably just me working on one of my sculptures. / 如果你听到我的小屋里传出砰砰的声音，那可能是我在制作石膏。",
        "divorced": "I've realized I'm happier by myself. So just leave me be.$u / 我觉得我一个人就挺开心的。所以就让我这样吧。$u",
        "Fri6": "Sometimes, a strange feeling comes over me. My head becomes totally empty... and I feel completely at peace, even blissful. / 有时候我会陷入一种奇怪的感觉，大脑一片空白……感觉特别平静，甚至有点幸福。#$e#Hey, now! It has nothing to do with drinking wine!$h / 喂！这跟喝酒没关系！$h",
        "Sun8": "If you ever find any interesting looking driftwood, I could use it. / 如果你有找到样貌有趣的浮木的话，我可能会用的着。#$e#It would be special that you gave it to me. / 从你那里得到这样的礼物真的很特别。",
        "winter_Thu6": "*Sigh*... It's hard to get fresh food in the winter. / *唉*……冬天里很难找到新鲜的食物。#$e#I bet your farm is pretty well stocked with food, huh? / 我猜你的农场里应该过得挺好的吧，是不是装满了食物？",
        "summer_Fri": "You can use a tapper to harvest syrups and other useful liquids directly from trees. / 用开孔器可以直接从树上收集糖浆或是其他有用的液体。#$e#It's a slow process, but the result can be quite valuable. / 这是个缓慢的过程，但是却有可能收获很珍贵的东西。",
        "fall_Thu6": "One of these days I'll have to make you a wild mushroom stir-fry.$h / 等哪天有时间，我要给你做一份炒野生菌。$h",
        "Fri4": "Hello, @. It's a nice day, isn't it? / 您好，@。今天天气真好，不是吗？#$e#Stop by my cabin if you ever need someone to talk to.$h / 如果你想找人聊天的话，就来我的小屋坐坐吧。$h",
        "Tue": "Hello, neighbor. / 邻居，你好啊。#$e#We both live outside of town. Does that mean something? / 我们都住在镇子外面。这是不是意味着什么呢？",
        "FlowerDance_Accept_Spouse": "Finally! I was starting to get worried you wanted to dance with someone else!$h / 吓我一跳！我还以为你是想和别人跳舞呢！$h",
        "dating_Leah_memory_oneday": "Please don't feel like you have to spend all your time with me now that we're dating... I know you're a busy person! / 虽然我们谈恋爱了，但你也不用整天跟我待在一起……我知道你很忙的！",
        "Mon_old": "$p 21#So are you making as much money as you hoped? / 那么你赚的钱有你预想的那么多吗？|Spending time in nature is very rewarding. / 呆在大自然里是非常有益的。",
        "Resort_Wander": "Mmm, I bet the trees around here would make for an interesting medium to work with. / 唔，这里的树木肯定能够成为非常有趣的原材料，值得雕琢一番。#$e#Though Willy probably wouldn't be happy with me if I dragged a bunch of logs onto his ship!$h / 但如果我把一大堆圆木拖到威利的船上，他恐怕会生我的气！$h",
        "dating_Leah": "I had a feeling you would ask me...$l / 我之前有预感你会来约我……$l",
        "AcceptGift_(O)200": "Mmm... Back in the city, the veggies never tasted this fresh. I love it!$h / 嗯……以前吃城里的蔬菜，哪里有现在这么新鲜，我很喜欢！$h",
        "married_Shane": "I'm happy that Shane's in such a good place. I've never seen him smile so much! / 谢恩过得这么好，我很高兴。我从没见过他笑得这么开心！#$e#With his love for chickens, I'm sure he'll fit right in on %farm Farm!$h / 他这么喜欢养鸡，肯定很适合待在%farm农场！$h",
        "event_parents1": "You're right... I just wouldn't have been happy back there.$u / 你说的没错……就算回到过去我也不会开心的。$u#$b#It was better for both of us... to end an unsustainable relationship while we were still young and flexible.$u / 这对我们两个来说都比较好……趁我们还年轻，还有办法改变的时候结束这段难以维系的感情。$u",
        "eventSeen_584059_memory_oneday": "If my art continues to sell online like it has, I'll be able to keep making art forever. That's always been my dream. / 如果我的作品在网上能维持现在的销量，我就能一直创作了。这是我长久以来的梦想。",
        "summer_Mon": "I found some wild fruits this morning! / 我今天早上找到了一些野生的果子！#$e#Sorry, I don't have any left.$s / 抱歉，没有剩下的了。$s#$e#Keep looking, I'm sure you'll find something. / 继续找，我相信你会找到点什么的。",
        "fall_Fri": "Do you have a kitchen in your house? / 你房子里面有厨房吗？#$e#If you have a kitchen, you can cook all kinds of delicious meals.$h / 如果你有厨房的话，你可以自己动手做各种各样的美食了呢。$h",
        "married_Elliott": "Elliott's a real romantic... I'm sure your days will be filled with poetry!$h / 艾利欧特真的很浪漫……你的生活肯定会充满诗意！$h",
        "Sat": "I love to decorate for the different seasons. / 我很喜欢根据季节来进行装饰。",
        "winter_Mon": "I love the way everything looks when it's covered with fresh snow. / 我很喜欢一切都被新雪覆盖住的样子。",
        "Fri": "It's simpler to be friends with the trees. They don't have much to say.$h / 和树当朋友比较简单。它们没什么话讲。$h",
        "Resort_Leaving": "Well, that was deeply relaxing. / 嗯，真是轻松愉快。",
        "Resort_Bar": "Have you tried the Piña Colada? I'm on my second one... hehe. / 你试过椰林飘香鸡尾酒了吗？我已经喝第二杯了……嘿嘿。",
        "fall_Fri6": "Stop by my cabin if you ever need someone to talk to.$h / 如果你想找人聊天的话，就来我的小屋坐坐吧。$h",
        "summer_Thu6": "I have a good eye for wild fruit. Some day I'll make you a nice fruit salad.$h / 我的眼睛擅长于发现野生的果子。以后我要为你做美味的水果沙拉。$h"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/Leo",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "Sun": "When it rains, strange birds visit. / 在下雨的时候，会有陌生的鸟儿来访。#$b#I try to speak to them... but they fly away.$s / 我试着跟它们说话……但它们飞走了。$s#$b#I guess they don't want to be friends...$s / 我猜，它们不想交朋友……$s",
        "Wed": "...Sorry... I'm shy today.$3 / ……抱歉……我今天有点不好意思。$3",
        "Thu": "Have you met the others like you? / 你有见过其他那些和你一样的人吗？#$b#I don't talk to them much. I feel safer with my own kind...$3 / 我不怎么跟他们说话，和我自己的同类待在一起，我感觉更安全……$3",
        "Tue": "When Sun is angry, it feels good in the jungle. / 太阳发怒、烈日当头的时候，待在丛林中就很舒服。#$e#Sun can't find us beneath the leaves. We trick him! Haha...$h / 躲在叶子下面，太阳就找不到我们了。我们把他给耍了！哈哈……$h",
        "AcceptGift_(O)StardropTea": "Wow, tastes just like golden walnuts! This is great! / 哇，这个味道跟金核桃一样！太神奇了！",
        "Sat": "...I'm sad today.$s / ……我今天很伤心。$s#$e#You go on... have fun. Let me be sad.$s / 你继续……找乐子吧。让我伤心就好。$s",
        "Mon": "Hi... Everything okay? / 嗨……一切都好吗？",
        "Fri": "One time... I was at the top of the volcano at night, and I saw lights far, far away. / 有一天晚上……我在火山顶端，我看到远处有光亮。#$b#I wonder if there are other bird families out there?$3 / 我想知道，那里是不是住着其他的鸟儿家族？$3",
        "Wed2": "Be careful in the volcano... the spirits don't like outsiders. / 在火山里要小心……精灵不喜欢外来者。",
        "Fri4": "I wonder if I could see your home from the top of the volcano? / 我在想，站在火山顶上能不能看见你的家？",
        "AcceptGift_(TR)ParrotEgg": "This is a precious egg... A baby! I'm glad you brought it to me, I'll keep it safe. / 这个蛋很珍贵……里面可是一个小宝宝！谢谢你把它带给我，我会好好照顾的。",
        "Mon4": "I've learned a lot from my parrot family... / 从我的鹦鹉家族那里，我学到了很多东西……#$b#But I'm sure there's a lot more out there I don't know.$s / 但我很确定，在外面的世界里还有更多我不知道的东西。$s"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/LeoMainland",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "Fri8": "Uncle Linus says I should 'cook' my fish before eating it...$s / 莱纳斯叔叔说我应该把鱼先“烹饪”了再吃……$s#$b#I'm having a hard time getting used to it... so dry...$s / 这太难适应了……干巴巴的……$s",
        "GreenRain": "I like this weather... it's so humid. It reminds me of the forest back home. / 我很喜欢这个天气……很潮湿，仿佛回到了我家乡的森林。",
        "Sun10": "The parrots want me to thank you for all the golden walnuts you've found. They're really enjoying them.$h / 鹦鹉们想让我感谢你给它们找到那么多金色核桃。它们觉得很好吃。$h",
        "Thu": "Have you ever noticed all the interesting birds that live here? / 你有没有注意过，生活在这里的各种有趣鸟儿？#$e#If you listen closely, they might tell you something. / 如果你听得足够仔细，它们也许会告诉你一些东西。",
        "Tue": "Miss Penny is doing her best to get me up to speed in my schooling. She's really nice... / 潘妮小姐正在尽力让我加快学习的速度。她真是个好人……#$e#...Luckily, I remember some things from my old, old life... before washing up on the island... so it's not as difficult as it could be. / ……幸运的是，我回想起了一些事情，来自我过去的过去……在我流落到岛上之前……所以，学习也没有想象中的那么难。#$e#Miss Penny says she's impressed with how much I know! / 潘妮小姐说，她很惊讶我知道那么多的东西！",
        "AcceptGift_(O)StardropTea": "Wow, tastes just like golden walnuts! This is great! / 哇，是金色核桃的味道！真好喝！",
        "LeoDeparture": "I need to find some place to live...$s / 我需要找到能够居住的地方……$s#$b#But I have a plan... I'm going to rely on my friends. / 但我有个计划……我打算依靠我的朋友们。",
        "Mon": "Hey, @. Nice to see you back on the island, just like old times. This is fun! / 你好，@。能再在岛上见到你，就跟从前一样，真是太好了。我很开心！#$e#You know, I was scared when you first arrived... I knew my life was about to change.$u / 嗯，当初你第一次来的时候，我被吓到了……当时我就感觉我的生活会发生变化。$u",
        "18": "When I first arrived, Linus made me a suit out of leaves, like his... / 我刚来的时候，莱纳斯给我做了一套叶子衣服，就和他的衣服一样……#$b#But I looked funny... like a fuzzy mango!$h / 但我穿着看上去很滑稽……像一只毛茸茸的芒果！$h#$e#I think I'll stick to my feathers. / 我想，我还是继续用羽毛就好。",
        "Thu10": "I felt like a stranger here, at first. But I've made a lot of friends!$h / 最初，我感觉自己在这里是个外来者。但我已经交到了许多朋友！$h#$b#For once, I feel like I belong... / 终于，我感觉自己有了归属……",
        "Sun": "You know, Stardew Valley might be my new home... but the island will always be my home, too. / 也许我会把星露谷当作我的新家……但是，这座岛也始终会是我的家。#$e#It's nice to be able to come back and visit. / 能够回来看看，真是不错。",
        "Wed": "Between Linus and Miss Penny, I'm going to learn everything there is to learn!$h / 莱纳斯和潘妮小姐会让我学到所有需要学习的东西！$h#$e#Mayor Lewis says I'm on the fast track to becoming a 'well-rounded citizen'... whatever that means. / 刘易斯镇长说，我就快要成为“全方位发展的镇民”了……虽然我不懂是什么意思。",
        "4": "I saw a big mango floating in the sky. Linus told me it was a hot-air balloon!$u / 我看到一个大芒果飘在空中。莱纳斯告诉我说，那是个热气球！$u#$b#I thought only birds could fly... / 我还以为只有鸟儿能飞呢……",
        "Thu8": "It felt bad at first... to leave the island and set foot in a strange land.$s / 最初感觉很糟……要离开岛屿，然后踏上一片陌生的土地。$s#$e#But, I got used to it after a while. / 但，过了一段时间后，我就适应了。#$b#I'm a very flexible person!$h / 我真是个适应性极强的人！$h",
        "Sat": "Maybe some day, I'll visit Zuzu City...$u / 也许有一天，我会去参观一下祖祖城……$u#$b#But I'm not even close to being ready, yet. This world is already so strange to me, and I'm very comfortable here right now!$h / 但现在我完全没有准备好。对我来说，这里已经够陌生的了，不过目前我待在这里感觉很自在！$h",
        "Tue10": "I'm sure Jas and Vincent thought I was weird, at first. I accidentally squawked at the school table a few times... that didn't help.$s / 在一开始的时候，我确定贾斯和文森特觉得我很奇怪。我不小心在学习的桌子旁鸟叫了几次……很尴尬。$s#$e#It was a big change for everyone. But we're good friends now!$h / 大家都觉得我来了之后镇上的变化很大。但我们现在是好朋友了！$h",
        "Sat10": "@? Um... I'm a little embarrassed to ask...$u / @？呃……我有点不好意思问……$u#$b#But... do you think Jas would ever like a guy like me?$u / 你觉得……贾斯会跟我这样的人做朋友吗？$u#$b#Or am I too weird?$s / 我是不是太古怪了？$s#$e#Hahaha... who cares. I'll figure it out some day.$h / 哈哈哈……谁在乎呢。总有一天我会弄明白的。$h",
        "winter_Thu": "The birds of this valley don't mind the cold so much. / 山谷里的鸟儿并不太怕冷。#$e#I'm a little jealous of their warm coats...$s / 我有一点点嫉妒它们暖和的衣裳……$s",
        "Fri": "Linus has been teaching me about all the wild food in the valley. There's a lot of good stuff out here!$h / 莱纳斯一直在教我山谷里野生食物的各种知识。野外真是有不少好东西！$h#$e#Though... I do kind of miss having golden walnuts for breakfast every morning...$s / 不过……我确实有点怀念每天吃金色核桃当早餐的日子……$s",
        "winter_Fri": "Linus taught me how to make a special spice berry rubbed fish... / 莱纳斯教我制作了一种特殊的辣味梅子渍鱼……#$b#He says if I eat enough of it it'll keep me warm this winter!$h / 他说，只要我多吃点这种鱼，今年冬天我就不愁保暖了！$h"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/Lewis",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "winter_Fri6": "I've never been married. I have no family. All I live for is to be Mayor.$s / 我从未结婚。我没有家庭。我活着的意义就是当镇长。$s#$e#Is it worth it?$s / 这值得吗？$s#$e#...*sigh*...$s / ……*唉*……$s",
        "Thu": "The saloon can get pretty lively at night. Sometimes we even put a coin in the jukebox *chuckle*$h / 酒吧晚上的时候会挺热闹的。有时候我们甚至会往自动点唱机里放一枚硬币*窃笑*$h#$e#I like to visit once a week or so to catch up on things, anyway. / 不管怎么样，我每周都会去一次，去听听别人闲聊。",
        "divorced_twice": "Another divorce? C'mon, @... you should be a little more careful who you decide to marry in the future...$u / 又来离婚？@啊……你以后选择结婚对象的时候还是谨慎一点吧……$u",
        "summer_Thu": "The saloon gets pretty lively at night. / 酒吧晚上的时候挺热闹的。#$e#I like to visit once a week or so to catch up on things. And to get a taste of Gus' authentic spaghetti. / 我大概每周去一次，跟大家聊聊天。尝尝格斯的正宗意大利面。",
        "fall_Tue": "It was around this time of year when I first became Mayor, over twenty years ago. / 在 20 年以前，我也是在大概这个时候第一次当上镇长的。#$e#That makes me feel really old.$s / 真是感觉自己变老了啊。$s",
        "Introduction": "So, how was your first night in the old cottage? / 你在那个破屋里过的第一晚怎么样？#$e#Your grandpa used to complain about the rickety old bed. But I think, deep down, he actually loved that house. / 你爷爷以前总是抱怨那张晃晃悠悠的旧床。但我觉得，他心里其实是爱着那间房子的。",
        "summer_Sat": "Everyone seems a little happier on the weekends, don't you think? / 周末的时候大家看起来都比较开心，你不这么觉得吗？#$e#I'm on the job seven days a week, though. / 然而，我 7 天都在上班。",
        "Mon": "It's a good season to start thinking about gardening, even for us non-farmers. / 现在可是做园艺的好时节啊，甚至对我们这些不是农夫的人来说也一样。#$e# The valley is known for producing some of the finest spring flowers!$h / 星露谷因为出产最美的春季花卉而出名！$h",
        "movieTheater": "All the young people seem happy about the new movie theater. / 年轻人好像都挺喜欢电影院的。#$e#A thriving theater will be good for the local economy. I just hope there's nothing objectionable in those modern pictures! / 电影院生意好的话，对本地经济也有好处。我就希望这些新兴电影里面不要有大家反感的内容！",
        "joja_Begin": "So, the old Community Center is gone... I guess times change, and good things come and go... Yet I can't help but feel a sense of loss.$s / 所以，旧社区中心不见了……我猜时代在变，好东西来了又去……然而，我不禁有一点失落感。$s#$e#I just hope this doesn't mar my record as Mayor.$s / 我只希望这不会损害我作为市长的成绩。$s",
        "cropMatured_276": "Nothing says 'Fall' quite like a pumpkin, don't you think? / 看到南瓜成熟，就有“一叶知秋”的感觉了，是不是？",
        "cc_Bus": "@, did you hear? It seems the old town bus started working again overnight!$h / @，你听说了吗？似乎旧城巴士又开始在夜间运行了！$h#$b#That old thing has been dormant for decades... This is truly a great mystery. / 这旧东西几十年来一直处于休眠状态……这确实是一个很大的谜团。",
        "fall_Wed": "If you have any suggestions for the town, just drop a note into my suggestion box. / 如果你对镇子有什么建议的话，请往我的意见箱里投个小条子。#$e#Oh, that's right... I don't have a suggestion box. / 啊，对了……我都没有意见箱。",
        "Saloon_Entry": "Hi, Gus! / 嗨，格斯！",
        "Wed": "Hmm... tax collection... *mumble* ...spring festivities expenses... *mumble*...$u / 哼……收税……*嘟囔*……春季节日开销……*嘟囔*……$u#$e#Yes? / 怎么了？",
        "willyCrabs": "*sniff*... *sniff*... can you smell that? I've been catching hints of fresh crab all day...$u / *嗅*……*嗅*……你闻到了吗？我一整天一直都闻到新鲜螃蟹的味道……$u",
        "event_secret2": "*sob* ... I can't believe you would do that...$s / *啜泣*……我不敢相信你居然会做这种事……$s#$b#You're terrible.$s / 你真卑鄙。$s",
        "cropMatured_24": "Hey, I was doing my nightly rounds, and noticed that your first parsnip was ready. Congratulations! / 哎，我昨晚路过出货箱，发现你的第一批欧防风已经成熟了，祝贺你！",
        "AcceptBirthdayGift_Positive": "Ah, you remembered the old mayor's birthday. That's very thoughtful of you. And it's a nice gift!$h / 嚯，你还记得我这个老镇长的生日啊。你有心了，这个礼物我很喜欢！$h",
        "Resort_Chair": "Hehe... look at this place! I don't know how you did it, but this little vacation spot is the talk of the town.$h / 嘿嘿……看看这地方！我不知道你是怎么做到的，整个镇子竟然都在讨论这个小小的度假区了。$h",
        "pamHouseUpgrade": "@, I heard what you did for Pam and Penny... now *that's* the kind of community support I love to see in Pelican Town!$h / @，我听说了你为潘姆和潘妮做事……现在*这正是*我在鹈鹕镇乐见的那种社区支助！$h",
        "cc_Complete": "I've never felt such an overwhelming pride in our community. You've done Pelican Town a great service, @.$h / 我从未在我们的社区感受到如此巨大的自豪感。你为鹈鹕镇所做的服务真是太棒了，@。$h",
        "winter_Fri": "I hope things are going well for you on the farm. / 我希望你农场上一切都好。",
        "spring_3": "Have you planted any spring crops yet? The season doesn't last forever, you know. / 你开始种春天的作物了吗？时间可不等人哦。",
        "winter_Sun": "Hi there, @! How're you doing today?$h / 你好啊！@！今天怎么样？$h#$e#If you see Marnie, tell her I say 'hi'. / 如果你看到玛妮的话，帮我向她问声好。",
        "GreenRain": "I just got off the phone with the Governor... Apparently this rain is supposed to be completely harmless. Just an unusual phenomenon of nature. / 我刚刚打电话跟州长确认了……据说这场雨是完全无害的，只是大自然的一种奇异现象。#$b#Still, some of the townsfolk are panicking, which is never good... / 不过镇上还是有居民感到恐慌，这就不太好了……",
        "fall_Mon": "Some of the townsfolk are wary of strangers. You'll have to win their trust before they open up to you. / 镇子里有些人对陌生人很警惕。在他们对你坦诚之前，你得先赢得他们的信任。#$e#Just be persistent and you'll get through to them.$h / 只有坚持不懈，你才能接近他们。$h",
        "AcceptGift_(O)StardropTea": "I've sampled many teas in my life, but none are quite so rare and special as this. Thanks! / 我品尝过很多不同的茶，但还是这个茶最珍贵、最特别。谢谢你！",
        "summer_Tue": "How did I become Mayor in the first place? It's a long story. / 我一开始怎么当上镇长的？这个故事可说来话长了。#$e#We're both too busy for stories right now. / 咱俩现在都挺忙的，不适合讲故事。",
        "summer_Town_57_40": "#$c .3#Ah, my flowers are growing wonderfully!$h#$c .3#Good morning! Can you smell the sweet scent of these dew-lilies? / #$c .3#啊，我的花长的真好！$h#$c .3#早啊！你有闻到这些露水百合甜美的味道吗？#$e#It's early but the air is already quite warm. Summer is nice for an old guy like me hehe. / 现在还早，但是天气已经挺热的了。嘿嘿，夏天很适合像我这样的老人。",
        "Resort_Shore": "Vacation opportunities like this could really expand the local economy! / 这种度假的机会能够很有效地带动当地经济！#$e#I'd better not stay in the sun too long, or my moustache will dry out. / 我最好还是不要在太阳里待太久，不然我的胡子就会干掉。",
        "winter_1": "Well, winter is here! That means the townspeople will be spending most of their days indoors. / 好吧，冬天来了！这意味着镇子里的人大部分时间都会呆在屋子里。#$e#At least you'll know where to find them!$h / 至少你知道哪儿能找到他们！$h",
        "wonGrange": "Congrats on winning that grange display competition. / 恭喜你在农庄展览中获胜。#$e#Hehe... Just between you and me, I think Pierre needed a bowl of humble pudding!$h / 嘿嘿……我私底下跟你说哦，我觉得是该挫一挫皮埃尔的锐气！$h",
        "event_secret1": "Thank you @. I won't forget this. / 谢谢你，@。我是不会忘记这事的。",
        "summer_Sun": "Say, are you growing any blueberries on your farm? / 你有没有在你的农场里种蓝莓呢？#$e#I do enjoy a fresh blueberry.%revealtaste:Lewis:258 / 我是真的很喜欢新鲜的蓝莓。%revealtaste:Lewis:258",
        "fall_Sun": "Are you doing your best on the farm, @? You'll have to accomplish things in many areas if you want to become a well-rounded citizen. / 你有在农场上认真干活吗，@？为了成为一个十全十美的市民，你得在许多领域上都取得成就才行啊。",
        "fall_Thu": "The saloon gets pretty lively at night. / 酒吧晚上的时候挺热闹的。#$e#I like to visit once a week or so to catch up on things. / 我喜欢大概每周去一次，跟大家聊聊天。",
        "GreenRain_2": "I guess we can expect these unusual rains every year. I think everyone is a little calmer knowing that it's just part of nature. / 我估计这种奇怪的雨每年都会下了。大家意识到这只是大自然的现象之后应该也镇定了很多。",
        "divorced_once": "The divorce paperwork is all squared away. Sorry that things didn't work out... / 离婚手续已经办理好了。你们的事情不顺利，我很遗憾……",
        "winter_Wed": "I'll still come by every night to collect your produce, even in the snow. / 我每天晚上都会来收你的产品，就算下雪也不会耽误。#$e#You still need to make money in the winter! / 在冬天你也得赚钱嘛！",
        "Tue2": "At the start of each season you'll have to remove the previous season's dead crops. It's easiest with a scythe. / 每个季节伊始，你都得先除掉上个季节的死掉的作物。用镰刀是最方便的。",
        "Resort": "I'm impressed, @. You've really fixed up the place!$h / @，你太了不起了。你真的把这个地方给修好了！$h",
        "fall_Town_57_40": "#$c .3#Hmmm... these strange little mushrooms have been popping up in my wood chips. I wonder what kind they are?#$c .3#Good morning! We're slowly entering the cold months, so I'm seeing my garden to a gentle end. / #$c .3#唔……我的木材里面开始长奇怪的小蘑菇了。不知道能不吃？#$c .3#早啊！最近天气转凉，我也打算整理一下花园过冬了。#$e#Ah, you're in town early, huh? Finished with your farm chores already? / 你今天来得挺早嘛。农活已经做完了吗？",
        "cc_Bridge": "Somehow, that old bridge to the quarry is now repaired. / 通往采石场的断桥莫名其妙修好了。#$b#I'm shocked... It must've taken a whole team to fix that thing! / 我挺吃惊的……这得来一整队人，才能修好吧！#$b#Who could've done that? / 会是谁干的？",
        "winter_Tue": "I've got to start coming up with a plan for improving our town next year! / 我得想出一个计划，在下一年中帮助我们的镇子发展！",
        "cropMatured_254": "Those melons have been looking real good over at %farm farm!$h / %farm农场的甜瓜长势很好啊！$h#$b#You know, that was one of your grandpa's favorite crops back in the day. / 哈哈，当时你爷爷可喜欢种甜瓜了。",
        "GreenRainFinished": "Well, that was quite the excitement for our little town! I'm just relieved that everyone is okay.$h / 哎，也算是让我们的小镇躁动了一番！幸好大家都没事。$h#$e#If this ever happens again, I think we'll all be a little more relaxed. It's not the end of the world! / 假如再发生一次的话，大家应该会从容不少——这又不是世界末日！",
        "cc_Begin": "*sniff*... *sniff*... Ah, I sense you've been spending some time in the old Community Center. It's good to know someone's taking care of the place. / *嗅*……*嗅*……啊，我感觉你已在旧社区中心呆了一段时间。真是太好了，有人在照料那个地方。",
        "spring_10": "Ah... There's nothing like a strong cup of tea in the morning. / 啊……没什么比得上清晨的一杯浓茶了。",
        "Sun": "I've been Mayor of Pelican Town for over twenty years! / 我在鹈鹕镇当了 20 多年的镇长！#$e#No one ever runs against me when it's time for an election. I like to think that it means I'm doing my job well. / 选举的时候，没一个人投我的反对票。我觉得那意味着我的工作做得很好。#$e#I like being Mayor. / 我喜欢当镇长。",
        "fall_Wed2": "Every Wednesday I have buckwheat waffles and coffee for breakfast. It's a little tradition I observe to keep the bachelor life interesting.$h / 每周三早上我都要吃荞麦华夫饼配咖啡。这是我为了让单身的日子更有趣些而定下的规矩。$h",
        "married": "Congratulations, @. This is a big step forward for you and %spouse. You've really grown some roots in this town! / @，这是你和%spouse向前迈出的重要一步，祝贺你们。你也算是在这个小镇上扎根了！",
        "summer_Fri": "Hmm... I wonder if it's anyone's birthday today? I'd better check the calendar by Pierre's shop. / 嗯……今天是不是什么人的生日？我最好去看看皮埃尔商店的日历。",
        "Tue": "Just place anything you want to sell in the shipping box next to your house. / 把你想要卖掉的东西都放到你房子旁边的包装箱里。#$e#I'll be interested in seeing what kinds of things you put in there. / 我会去看看你往里面放了什么的。",
        "AcceptBirthdayGift_Negative": "Ah, you remembered the old mayor's birthday... what's this?$h / 嚯，你还记得我这个老镇长的生日啊……这是什么东西？$h#$b#Um... well you know what they say, 'it's the thought that counts'. / 呃……这个嘛，心意到了就行了。",
        "Saloon": "Good evening! It's nice to see you socializing with the townsfolk. / 晚上好！真高兴看到你在和镇子里的人聊天。#$b#It's good to stop by once in a while and see what the latest news is.$h / 每隔一段时间就来这里坐坐，听听新闻也挺好的。$h",
        "summer_Wed": "The moonlight jellies will be here soon. It's one of my favorite things about the valley. / 月光水母就快出来了。那玩意儿可是我在星露谷里最喜欢的东西之一。",
        "Town_57_40": "#$c .3#You're in town early, huh? Finished with your farm chores already? / #$c .3#你这么早就来镇子里了，嗯？农活已经做完了吗？#$e#Good morning! I'm just checking on the garden as usual.$h#$c .5#Hmm... are these aphids?$s / 早啊！我还是在像往常一样检查花园而已。$h#$c .5#嗯……这些是蚜虫吗？$s#$e#Hmm... I hope these aren't scale bugs...$s / 嗯……但愿可别是蚧壳虫啊……$s",
        "summer_Mon": "Gardening is a hobby of mine, so I'm excited for this warm weather. / 园艺是我的爱好之一，因此我很喜欢这种温暖的天气。",
        "fall_12": "Do you have any bee houses on your farm? / 你农场里有蜂巢吗？#$e#If you place them near flowers you can get different types of honey. / 如果你把蜂巢放在鲜花旁边的话，你就能得到各种各样的蜂蜜了。",
        "fall_Fri": "I hope things are going well for you on the farm. / 我希望你农场上一切都好。",
        "fall_Fri4": "Have you tried Gus' 'secret' spaghetti sauce?$s / 你有没有尝过格斯的“秘制”意大利面酱？$s#$b#...The ingredients may be secret, but the smell isn't. / ……成分也许是个秘密，但是它的味道不是。#$b#I'll see you later. / 回头见啦。",
        "pamHouseUpgradeAnonymous": "@, did you hear? Someone paid Robin to build Pam and Penny a house! Robin won't tell me who it was, though. / @，你听说了吗？有人付钱给罗宾，让他为潘姆和潘妮建了房子！不过，罗宾不会告诉我那人是谁。#$e#Regardless of who paid, I love seeing this kind of community support in Pelican Town!$h / 无论谁付了钱，我都乐见鹈鹕镇有这样的社区支助！$h",
        "married_twice": "Congratulations once again, @. / @，再次祝贺你。",
        "Sat": "Everyone seems a little happier on the weekends, don't you think? / 周末的时候大家看起来都比较开心，你不这么觉得吗？#$e#I'm on the job seven days a week, though. / 然而，我 7 天都在上班。",
        "winter_Mon": "Another year is almost over! / 今年又要过完了！#$e#I hope you had a productive year! / 我希望你下一年能够丰收！",
        "Fri": "I hope things are going well on %farm farm. I'd hate to see it all dried up. / 我希望%farm农场上一切都好。我不想看到它干透了的样子。",
        "Resort_Leaving": "Everyone aboard! We're heading back to the valley! / 大家快上船！我们要回星露谷了！",
        "Saloon4": "Good evening, @! I'm glad to see you relaxing at the saloon. It's good for you to take a break now and then.$h / 晚上好，@！真高兴看到你在这里休息。偶尔休息休息对你有好处的。$h#$b#Your grandfather always worked himself too hard... I'll have an extra beer in his honor tonight. / 你的祖父总是太努力工作了……我今晚要多喝一杯啤酒，向他致敬。",
        "fall_19": "Sometimes you can tell if there's something buried underground. Just keep your eyes open. / 有时候，如果地底下埋着什么东西的话，你能直接看出来。注意观察就行了。",
        "Resort_Bar": "Hehe... Gus is really in his element. / 嘿嘿……格斯真是得心应手啊。"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/Linus",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "GreenRain_2": "I've already gathered enough moss for the entire year. How about you? / 我收集了很多苔藓，够用一年了，你呢？",
        "summer_Tue4": "How have you been, my young friend? / 你最近怎么样啊，年轻的朋友？",
        "winter_Sat4": "Thanks for stopping by. I was actually feeling a little lonely this morning. / 谢谢你来看我。我今天早上还真感觉有些寂寞呢。#$e#So, have you discovered anything interesting in the mines? / 你有在矿洞里面找到什么有趣的东西吗？",
        "Thu": "...Hmm? Do you want something from me? / ……嗯？你有什么想要的吗？",
        "Introduction": "A stranger?... Hello. / 陌生人？……你好。#$e#Don't mind me. I just live out here alone. / 不要在意我。这里就只有我一个人住。",
        "AcceptGift_(O)166": "No, thank you. I have no desire for money... In fact, I think it's cursed. [166] / 不用了，我不需要钱……要我说，那可是万恶之源。[166]",
        "eventSeen_8357109": "The water here comes from glaciers high up in the mountains. / 这里的水来自山顶上的冰川。#$e#I traveled to the source once, just to pay my respects to the water. / 我曾经去过一次水源，为了向水表示敬意。",
        "reject_869": "What do you have there? Looks like it would make good bait.$h / 你拿着的是什么？看起来是不错的鱼饵原料。$h",
        "Mon": "The crisp air of the wilderness is all I care to know. / 我想要的就是野外清新的空气。#$e#I live out here by choice. / 我住在这外面是我自己的选择。",
        "movieTheater": "Movie theater? Hmm... for me, the slow procession of nature is all the drama I need. / 电影院吗？唔……对我来说，大自然的万物变迁就是最好的演出了。",
        "summer_Thu4": "I have my own reasons for living alone like this. / 我像这样一个人住，是有自己的原因的。#$e#Some things are best left unsaid... / 有些事情还是不说为好……#$e#I should do some foraging. / 我应该找点东西吃了。",
        "summer_Wed6": "Ah... summer. The warm sun heats up the cans for me. / 啊……夏天。温暖的阳光能帮我加热这些罐头。#$b#Then at night I've got a warm meal to look forward to. / 然后晚上的时候，我就可以有热乎饭吃了。",
        "MovieInvitation": "Oh... me? I usually wouldn't, but... okay. It's nice of you to think about me. / 哎……我吗？我一般不会去那边，不过……好吧。你能想着我，真是太贴心了。#$b#I'll head over there in a little while. / 我一会儿就过去。",
        "summer_Mon4": "During all these years I've discovered a few secrets about life. / 这么多年来，我发现了一些生命的奥秘。#$e#You'll have to find out for yourself. / 你得自己去寻找。",
        "winter_Tue4": "Thanks for not shunning me, @. It takes a lot of wisdom to override your base instincts. / 谢谢你没有回避我，@。忽略自己的本能是需要很多智慧的。#$e#I'm a human like everyone else. I just have a different lifestyle. / 我和其他人一样。我只是有着不同的生活方式罢了。",
        "Wed2": "I have to be wary of strangers. Most people don't like a 'wild man'. / 我得对陌生人保持警惕。大部分人不喜欢“野人”。",
        "GreenRainFinished": "How did the moss harvest go? Hehe... My bed is a lot softer now. / 你的苔藓采集得怎么样？嘿嘿……拜其所赐，我的床蓬松多了。",
        "summer_Sat4": "You can find rainbow trout in streams right now. / 你现在能在河里找到虹鳟鱼。",
        "fall_Wed4": "I don't have many responsibilities, so I spend my time thinking. / 我是无事一身轻，所以我把时间都花在思考上。#$e#You have to understand your thoughts before you can control them. / 你必须在你能控制自己的想法之前弄清楚它们。",
        "winter_Mon4": "After you've truly unplugged from the modern way of life, you'll start to really enjoy the simple things... like the sun, a ripe fruit, or finding a stick with the exact shape you were looking for. / 真正脱离现代的生活方式之后，你会开始喜欢上朴素的东西……比如阳光、熟透了的水果，有时还能正好找到一根形状奇特的木棍。",
        "Sun": "#$1 linusVandal#Someone was throwing rocks at my tent last night... I just had to wait it out.$s / 昨天晚上有人朝我的帐篷扔石头……我只能等他们扔完。$s$k#$e#I don't like to stay in one place for too long. There's just too much to experience in the world. / 我不喜欢在一个地方呆太长的时间。世界上有太多有意思的事情可以去经历了。",
        "winter_Wed4": "I'm sure you understand why I'm cautious of strangers. / 我相信你一定知道我为什么对陌生人保持警惕。#$e#But let's put that in the past, okay? You and I are friends now, I think. / 不过这事就翻篇吧，好吗？我想我们现在是朋友了。",
        "Wed": "I don't know you well enough to trust you. Sorry. / 我不够了解你，所以没办法信任你。抱歉。",
        "DumpsterDiveComment": "Find anything good?$h / 找什么好东西没？$h",
        "AcceptGift_(O)Book_Trash": "I don't usually read books... But this one is right up my 'alley'... Thank you!$h / 我不太看书……不过这本正合我“口味”……谢谢你！$h",
        "Sun4": "It would be nice if the townspeople could accept me for who I am.$s / 如果镇子里的人能够接受我的生活方式就好了。$s#$b#I like living out here in the open air. That's what they don't understand. / 我喜欢住在户外。他们就是不懂这点。",
        "married": "I thought about tying the knot, once. But now, I'm happily married to the wind rustling in the leaves, and the frogs croaking under the silver moon. / 我以前考虑过结婚，不过现在有风吹过树叶沙沙作响，皎洁的月光下有青蛙呱呱叫，我也算有伴了。",
        "Fri4": "You can learn a lot from trees. / 你能从树木中学到很多东西。#$b#Spend time with them and they might tell you their secrets. / 多和它们相处，它们也许就会告诉你它们的秘密。#$e#Go in peace, young one. / 安静地去吧，年轻人。",
        "AcceptGift_Positive_category_greens": "That's a good find! I'm always happy when eating wild food. Thank you. / 这个东西真不错！吃野生采集的东西我总是很高兴。谢谢你。",
        "mineArea_80": "Very few people have gone as deep into the mines as you have. / 很少有人能像你这样到达矿井这么深的地方。",
        "winter_Sun": "Sleeping on the ground is good for my back. / 在地板上睡觉对我的背有好处。#$e#It's best to look at the positive side of things.$h / 看待事情还是积极点好啊。$h",
        "GreenRain": "All these strange trees will be gone tomorrow... it's one of the mysteries of nature. / 这些奇怪的树明天就会全部消失……这就是大自然的奥秘。",
        "fall_Mon": "I've explored deep into the caves. / 洞穴里很深的地方我都有探索过。#$e#They hold some hidden secrets. / 这些山洞有一些隐藏的秘密。#$e#Just be cautious if you go in there. / 进去那里面的话一定要小心。",
        "summer_Fri4": "Whenever you catch a fish, take a moment to thank it for its sacrifice. / 当你抓到一条鱼的时候，要花一秒钟去感谢它所做出的牺牲。#$b#Even if you don't believe in the spirit of the fish, it's a good mental exercise. We need to be aware of our effect on the environment. / 即使你不相信鱼有灵魂，这也是很好的精神锻炼。我们需要了解我们对环境的影响。",
        "Tue": "...Have you come to ridicule me? / ……你是来嘲笑我的吗？#$e#I'm just minding my own business. / 我只是专注于自己的事情而已。",
        "AcceptGift_(O)StardropTea": "This means a lot to me, @. I'll save it for a quiet day in the tent. Thank you! / @，你送我这个我真的很高兴，我会找一天坐在帐篷里安静品尝。谢谢你！",
        "Tue4": "You can learn to survive in the wild. I have. / 你可以学着在野外生存。我就是这样。#$e#I think we all have a hidden urge to return to nature. It's just a little scary to make the leap. / 我想我们心里都藏着一份想要回到大自然里的冲动。只是迈出那一步有点吓人而已。",
        "winter_Fri4": "The trees go to sleep during the winter. It makes it a bit lonely out here. / 树会在冬天的时候休眠，这会让我感觉有些寂寞。#$e#But I wouldn't deny them their beauty sleep.$h / 但是我不会否认它们睡觉时的美丽。$h",
        "cc_Boulder": "My old friend, the glimmering boulder, has moved on. It may not seem like an important event, but to me it's a big change. / 我的老朋友，闪闪发光的巨石，已翻开新篇章。虽然这可能并不是一件重要的事，但对我来说，这是一个巨大的变化。#$b#I'm happy for the old rock to see more of the world, though.$h / 不过，我乐意让老石头多看看这个世界。$h",
        "AcceptGift_Positive_category_fish": "Ah, that looks fresh. I'll be eating good tonight!$h / 啊，看起来很新鲜。今晚能饱餐一顿了！$h",
        "Thu4": "The people here seem nice, but they avoid me. / 这里的人看起来很友善，但是他们躲着我。#$e#People are afraid of the unknown.$u / 人们会对未知的事物感到害怕。$u",
        "Sat4": "I have everything I need to survive, and more. Nature plays a wonderful tune if you can only learn to listen. / 我具备生存所需的一切能力，甚至更多。如果你能学着去聆听，就能听见大自然发出的美妙旋律。",
        "summer_Mon": "#$1 LinusHeron#I saw a heron wading gracefully through the morning mist. Such are the treasures of a quiet life. / 今早有些起雾，我看见一只鹭鸟优雅地踏着雾气飞去。这大概就是小镇生活的好处之一吧。$k#$e#It's so easy to get caught up in the noise of modern life. Your best years will pass you by in a formless blur. That's why you've got to learn to slow down.  / 人们总是十分容易地被城市的喧嚣影响。匆匆忙忙地过了不知所以的几十年。所以说，还是慢一点，悠然一点生活更好。 ",
        "summer_Sun": "This is an easier time of year for me. I don't have to worry about staying warm. / 这个季节我还算能够过得舒服点。我不用担心取暖的事情。#$e#Plus, the fruits of the wild are growing everywhere. / 并且，野外到处都长着果子。",
        "Wed6": "I spend a lot of time thinking. / 我大部分时间都在思考。#$e#If you can fully understand the reasons behind your thoughts, you'll have reached a new level of being. / 如果你能完全理解你的想法背后的深层次原因，那么你就会达到一个全新的高度。",
        "Sat": "I'm happy by myself, you know. / 我一个人挺开心的。#$e#I don't need new friends. / 我不需要新朋友。",
        "fall_Sun": "I don't like to stay in one place for too long. / 我不喜欢在一个地方呆太长的时间。",
        "fall_Sun6": "There's nothing quite like a feast of wild mushrooms in the fall.$h / 没有什么比得上秋天里的一场蘑菇宴了。$h",
        "winter_Mon": "It can get really cold if you live in a tent.$s / 住在帐篷里真的非常冷。$s",
        "Fri": "Please don't destroy my tent. / 请不要弄坏我的帐篷。#$e#It's happened before.$s / 以前发生过这种事情。$s",
        "fall_Tue4": "#$1 LinusFall1#Some joker sprayed paint all over my home during the night... It took hours to scrub it off this morning. / 有些家伙晚上在我的房子四周到处喷颜料……今天早上我花了好几个小时才擦干净。$k#$e#I need to start gathering lumber for the winter. / 我得开始为过冬准备木材了。#$e#Do you have enough lumber to keep your house warm? / 你有没有为取暖准备足够的木头呢？",
        "winter_Thu4": "Winter is tough, but you can still fish and forage to get by. / 冬天很难熬，但是依然能够通过钓鱼和采集凑合着过。#$e#If you have any animals you should keep them inside. / 如果你有养动物的话，你应该把它们关在屋子里。",
        "AcceptGift_(O)774": "Let me see... it looks perfect. You're a good student, @.$h / 我看看……这个做得特别好。你学得很快啊，@。$h"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/Marnie",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "Saloon_Wed": "#$1 marnieAnimalSal#I spilled a whole bucket of milk on the floor today, it was horrible. And such a waste of my poor Belinda's hard work. / 我把一大篮牛奶都打翻了，太糟了。比琳达辛苦劳作的成果啊，真是浪费。$k$s#$e#It's nice of you to show up! It's a little more lively now. / 你来了就好！现在更热闹了。",
        "GreenRain_2": "The animals seems to enjoy this rain... I think it's putting extra nutrients into the grass. / 动物好像还挺喜欢这场雨的……可能是因为它让草料的营养增加了。",
        "Saloon_Tue": "There aren't very many people here today...$s / 今天人不太多呢……$s",
        "Resort": "Hehe... finally a chance to show off all my hard work at aerobics club.$h / 嘿嘿……终于有机会展示一下我在有氧健身俱乐部辛苦付出的成果了。$h",
        "Thu": "Hi. Need something? / 嗨。需要什么吗？#$e#I might be getting some different kinds of animals in the future. / 我以后可能会养些其他种类的动物。#$e#Although, I'll need to make sure there's a market for them, so you'll have to prove your skill with animals first. / 但是呢，我得确保他们能卖个好价钱，所以你要先加强自己的畜牧技术。#$e#Just keep treating your animals with respect and good things will happen. / 只要尊重对待你的动物们，总会有好事发生。",
        "Introduction": "Ah, Mayor Lewis told me you just arrived. I'm Marnie! / 啊，镇长刘易斯跟我说你刚到这里。我是玛妮！#$e#I sell livestock and animal care products at my ranch. You should swing by some time.$h / 我在我的牧场上卖家禽和动物护理用品。你有空的话可以来光顾一下哦。$h",
        "Fair_Judging": "Well, here goes nothing... / 那么，姑且一试吧……",
        "Saloon_Sun": "*sigh*... I wasn't very productive today. / *唉*……我今天不是很有效率。",
        "structureBuilt_Stable": "Oh, you got a horse? That's so wonderful! Horses are amazing animals.$h / 哦？你买了一匹马？那真是太好了！马儿是很了不起的动物。$h",
        "Mon": "I love animals, Mr. @. If you treat yours well I'm sure we'll become good friends! / 我爱动物，@先生。如果你好好对待你的动物的话，我相信我们能成为好朋友的！^I just love animals, Ms. @. Treat them kindly and we'll become friends, I'm sure! / 我真的爱动物，@女士。好好地对待你的动物，我们就能成为好朋友，一定能的！",
        "gotPet_memory_oneyear": "I just remembered... it's been about a year since you adopted %pet. I bet you two have grown really close by now! / 我突然想起来……你收养%pet已经有一年了吧，我猜它应该已经很亲近你了！",
        "GreenRainFinished": "Well, looks like we all got scared for nothing... The rain was totally harmless! / 哎，感觉根本没必要害怕嘛……这场雨根本没什么害处！",
        "Sun": "Hey there, it's good to see ya! / 嘿，很高兴见到你！#$e#Feel free to visit us any time you please. / 想什么时候来看我们都可以哦。",
        "Wed": "You can use a scythe to cut feed from grass. / 你可以使用镰刀割草来当饲料。#$e#Or you can buy it from me, of course!$h / 当然，你也可以从我这里买！$h#$e#I could use the cash...$u / 我正需要点钱……$u#$e#Adios. / 再见。",
        "Fri6": "I wonder if Mr. Lewis gets lonely in that big house of his... $s / 不知道刘易斯先生一个人住在那么大的房子里会不会孤单呢……$s#$e#It seems so empty in there, doesn't it? / 难道你不觉得那里空荡荡的吗？",
        "Resort_Chair": "Ew... the chair's wet. / 哎哟……椅子是湿的。",
        "Sun8": "Hi @!$h / 嗨，@！$h#$e#I'm glad we've become friends. I know I can trust you to take care of my dear animals. / 真高兴我们能成为朋友。我就知道可以把我可爱的动物们托付给你照顾。",
        "Saloon_Fri": "%Marnie doesn't seem to notice that you're there... / %玛妮好像没看到你……",
        "gotPet": "I think you'll love having a little friend on the farm with you. / 我相信农场上有了小动物陪伴你会很开心的。",
        "GreenRain": "You're not worried about this rain? That does put me at ease a little... / 你好像不是很担心这场雨？那我就稍微安心一点了……#$e#I just hope the cows tucked themselves in...$s / 但愿牛都躲好了，没有乱跑……$s",
        "Tue": "$query PLAYER_NPC_RELATIONSHIP any Shane married roommate#Now that Shane's gone, I'm going to have to teach Jas how to care for the chickens.|My nephew Shane has been staying at my place the last few months. / $query PLAYER_NPC_RELATIONSHIP any Shane married roommate#谢恩不住这里了，所以我只好开始教贾斯照看小鸡了。|我的侄子谢恩已经在我这待了几个月了。#$e#He helps me out with the chickens, so I'm not complaining. / 不过他会帮我养鸡，所以也没什么可抱怨的。",
        "AcceptGift_(O)StardropTea": "Wow, thanks a million, @. I won't forget this! / 哇，@，太感谢你了。我会一直记在心里的！",
        "Saloon": "Now that I'm here I can finally relax and socialize a bit. / 在这里，我终于能放松一下，聊聊天了。",
        "AcceptGift_(O)SkillBook_0": "Thanks, @. I always like to have a copy of the Almanac around. It's pretty accurate!$h / @，谢谢你，我一直想要一本年历，里面写的都很准！$h",
        "Resort_Shore": "Hee hee... It's interesting to see everyone in their bathing suits. / 嘻嘻……看到大家都穿着泳衣还挺好玩的。",
        "Saloon_Thu": "Phew! It sure feels good to kick back after a hard day's work. / 呼！努力工作了一天之后休息一下感觉真是不错。",
        "Mon4": "Animals are so innocent, so sweet. And If I don't look after them, who will?$s / 动物是如此的天真无邪，真好。如果我们不照顾它们，谁来照顾它们呢？$s#$e#I just hope my chickens aren't too upset when I take their eggs.$s / 但愿当我拿走鸡蛋的时候，母鸡们不会太难过。$s",
        "married_Shane": "I'm glad Shane's moving to your farm... he can keep the family tradition alive! / 谢恩搬到你的农场上去，我很高兴……或许他可以把家族传统传承下去！",
        "gotPet_memory_oneday": "I'm sure %pet will be a little shy at first. It takes a while for an animal to get comfortable in a new setting. / %pet一开始肯定会有点怕生，动物适应新环境总是需要一段时间的。",
        "Fair_Judged_PlayerLost_PurpleShorts": "That was some strange-looking purple lettuce in your grange display!$h / 你的农庄展览格子里放了些样子很奇怪紫色生菜啊！$h#$b#I swear, it looked just like Mayor Lewis' special und... $3 / 等等，这看起来像极了刘易斯镇长的内……$3#$b#Oh!... heh... never mind!$4 / 噢！……嘿嘿……没事！$4",
        "Thu_2": "You've been here a while, now... how's your farm doing? / 你已经在这儿呆了一段时间了，……现在你的农场怎么样了？#$e#Taking care of animals is easy as long as you don't forget about them!$h / 只要你不疏忽的话，照料动物其实是一件很简单的事！$h",
        "reject_789": "Gah!$4 / 呃啊！$4#$b#...Um... What? Heh.. I don't know what that is...$3 / ……嗯……什么？啊……我不知道那是什么……$3",
        "dating_Shane_memory_oneweek": "Shane seems a lot more positive and hopeful, lately. / 谢恩最近明显变得积极乐观了。#$b#I'm so happy you moved here, and that you two get along so well!$h / 幸好你搬到了这里，还跟他相处得那么好！$h",
        "Sat": "Have you been to that strange tower west of my house? / 你去过我家西边那个奇怪的高塔吗？#$e#One time I heard this terrible, otherworldly noise coming from there.$s / 有一次，我听到那里传来可怕、怪异的声响。$s#$e#I would avoid that place if I were you... / 我要是你的话就远远避开那个地方……",
        "Fri": "You can catch me at the saloon most nights. / 大多数晚上，你可以在酒吧找到我。#$e#Animals are great company, but I need to spend time with people, too. / 动物们是很好的同伴，但我也需要花时间和人们相处。",
        "Resort_Leaving": "I feel warm. / 我感觉很暖和。",
        "gotPet_memory_oneweek": "Has little %pet settled in yet? It's such a nice property for a pet to explore. / %pet它适应了吗？那个地方宠物肯定很喜欢探索。",
        "Resort_Bar": "Phew... It's hot!$s / 呼……真热！$s",
        "Fair_Judged": "Well, I didn't win... but it was still satisfying to share all my hard work! / 嗯，虽然我没有赢……但能和大家一起分享我辛勤劳作的成果，这也不错！",
        "Saloon_Sat": "I always see Clint here but he won't talk to anyone. He just glances over his shoulder now and then.$s / 我总能在这儿看到克林特，但是他不愿意和任何人说话。他总是时不时地回头瞅瞅。$s"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/Maru",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "summer_Tue4": "Sebastian hardly ever talks to me. I wonder if he even likes me at all? / 塞巴斯蒂安从来都不和我讲话。或许他是不喜欢我吧。#$e#It's sad, I want to have a brother but he doesn't act like one. / 挺让人难过的，我之前就一直想要个兄弟，但和他却生分得很。",
        "Mon6": "Sometimes my head gets so cluttered with nonsense I can hardly think. Does that ever happen to you? / 有时候我满脑子都在胡思乱想，都没法正常思考了。你有没有过这种情况？#$e#Getting some fresh air usually helps. / 去呼吸些清新空气就会好些了。",
        "winter_Fri6": "You look fresh today. I guess it's that crisp winter air. / 你今天看起来很潇洒哦。大概是冬日的飒爽空气所致吧。",
        "Resort_Entering": "Willy mentioned that you helped fix the boat. Thanks for doing that! / 威利说你帮忙修好了船。谢谢你！",
        "winter_Mon8": "Hi @!$h / 嗨，@！$h#$e#Hey, don't you think my snowman looks kind of like you? / 你看我堆的这个雪人，是不是有点像你？",
        "Resort_Towel_2": "We're so far removed from civilization out here. / 这里距离文明世界太遥远了。#$b#Imagine the stars you could see at night. / 想象一下你在晚上能看见的那些星星。#$e#Who knows, maybe we'd even see a flying saucer or two!$h / 说不定我们还能看到飞碟，谁知道呢！$h",
        "Thu": "I plan on spending a lot of time with my telescope this summer. / 今年夏天我准备多花些时间在我的望远镜上。",
        "summer_Thu": "Sorry, I was just thinking about some gadgets I'm making.#$q 35/36 Thu_01_old#I've decided I'm going to build a robot someday.#$r 35 30 Thu_0#That should be very easy for you.#$r 36 -50 Thu_01_01#You should be more realistic.#$r 35 40 Thu_01_02#It sounds challenging. / 抱歉，我只是在考虑最近正在制造的小玩意儿。#$q 35/36 Thu_01_old#我下了决心，以后一定要自己做个机器人出来。#$r 35 30 Thu_0#对你来说，应该是小菜一碟。#$r 36 -50 Thu_01_01#你可别眼高手低了。#$r 35 40 Thu_01_02#听起来应该挺难的吧。",
        "Sat8": "You know, I was thinking... even with all the technology in the world, nothing beats having a real human friend. / 我在想……即使世界上科技这么发达了，还是比不上有一个真实的人类朋友。",
        "Sun_01_02": "Yikes! I'm sorry. Have you ever thought of doing something different...?$s / 呀！对不起。你没想过做点其他的事情吗……？$s",
        "fall_Tue": "The trees look beautiful today!$h / 今天的树林看起来真的很美！$h",
        "Introduction": "Oh! Aren't you the one who just moved in? / 噢！你就是那个新搬来的人吧？#$b#I'm Maru. I've been looking forward to meeting you!$h / 我是玛鲁。我一直期待着和你见面！$h#$e#You know, with a small town like this, a new face can really alter the community dynamic. It's exciting! / 要知道，在这么小的镇子里，新面孔总会让社区热闹起来。真让人兴奋！",
        "summer_Sat": "Hey, have any interesting farm stories to tell me? / 最近农场上有什么好玩的事吗？#$e#Guess not. / 看来没有呢。",
        "Sat6": "If you think about the human body, it's hard to believe that somehow, it all just 'works'. / 一旦仔细想想人体的组成，就会觉得人能动起来这一点很不可思议。",
        "fall_Mon8": "You should come visit me at the clinic tomorrow. I work from 10 a.m. to 4 p.m.$h / 你明天应该来诊所看我。我的上班时间是早上 10 点到下午 4 点。$h",
        "Mon": "Whenever I'm struggling with a technical problem, I always take a walk. / 每当我遇到技术难题，我都会去散散心。#$e#It's surprising how much a change of scenery can help. / 换个风景居然能起到这么大的作用真是神奇。",
        "secondChance_Girls": "You've lost some respect with me, @... but I'm willing to forgive you.$s / 你让我无法再那么尊重你，@……但是我愿意原谅你。$s",
        "summer_1": "This is going to be a great season for stargazing. / 这个季节晚上看星星是最好不过了。",
        "FlowerDance_Decline": "I'm flattered! But... No. / 我受宠若惊！但是……不行。",
        "Sun_01_01": "Well that's good, isn't it?$h / 这很好，不是吗？$h",
        "fall_Wed4": "If you have any extra metal laying around, I could always use it for one of my projects. / 如果你有多余的金属块，可以分给我一些，我可以用在自己的研究上。#$e#But only if you don't need it yourself. / 啊，不过不要勉强，真的用不上再给我吧。",
        "fall_Wed": "Bleh... I don't feel like working tomorrow. / 唉唉……明天真的不想继续工作呢。",
        "Wed": "On Tuesdays and Thursdays I work at Harvey's clinic. / 周二和周四我会在哈维的诊所工作。#$b#He says he likes having me around in case his medical equipment goes haywire!$h / 他说他喜欢和我一起工作，万一医疗器械故障了我可以帮上大忙！$h#$e#Being a farmer must be pretty easy, huh? / 当个农夫应该很轻松吧？",
        "dumped_Girls": "You've got some nerve, speaking to me!$a / 你有些紧张，和我聊聊！$a",
        "event_robot_explain2": "I see. Well it wasn't a very funny joke.$a / 原来是这样。你这笑话还真是蹩脚。$a",
        "summer_Thu10": "How do your hands stay so soft with all that farm work? / 你天天做农活，手怎么还这么柔软？",
        "fall_Sat": "All these falling leaves will provide food for mushrooms and other small organisms.$u / 地上的落叶对于蘑菇和其它菌类的生长很有好处哦。$u#$e#Interesting, isn't it? / 怎么样，挺有意思的吧？",
        "AcceptBirthdayGift_Positive": "Hey, what's this, a birthday gift? It's great! Thanks for remembering me!$h / 哇，这是给我的生日礼物吗？我很喜欢！谢谢你记得我的生日！$h",
        "winter_Fri": "I hope I don't catch the flu this year. / 希望今年不要得流感才好。",
        "AcceptGift_(O)337": "Oh, wow! That's a rare element. It's theorized that all the iridium in our world comes from meteorites...$h / 哇！这可是稀有的元素，有人推测世界上所有的铱都来自陨石……$h",
        "Event_Space1": "It's amazing, isn't it? / 很神奇，不是吗？",
        "winter_Sun": "I get so sleepy when it's cold... / 天气这么冷，让人总想打瞌睡……",
        "GreenRain": "I want to go collect samples with my dad, but my Mom is insisting we stay here... / 我想跟我爸一起去采集样本，可是我妈非得要我跟她待在这里……",
        "fall_Mon": "Have you explored the mines much? I've heard you can find some useful materials there. / 你有没有去矿井那边看看？听说那里有很多有用的材料呢。",
        "breakUp": "Not good enough for you, huh?$a / 你觉得我不适合你，是吗？$a#$b#Fine...$s / 行……$s",
        "AcceptGift_(O)StardropTea": "Mmm... How does it taste so good? This is really a great gift. / 嗯……为什么会这么好喝？我很喜欢这个礼物。",
        "summer_Wed4": "Penny and I have been doing a seasonal book club. / 我和潘妮最近弄了一个短期的读书会。#$b#It's just the two of us, but it's still fun to discuss what we're reading! / 就我们两个人，不过聊聊读过的书还是很开心的！",
        "summer_Tue": "Sebastian is my half-brother, if you didn't know already. / 不知之前有没有和你讲过，其实塞巴斯蒂安是我同父异母的兄弟。#$e#We look totally different. / 不过我们俩长相是完全不同啦。",
        "fall_Tue2": "@, I just love how the trees look right now! / @，最近的树林还真是美丽呢！#$e#I know you like them too. / 你肯定也是这么认为的吧。",
        "winter_Sat": "Have you built a furnace yet? / 你有没有搭建熔炉？#$e#You can use them to turn raw material like ores into more useful products.$u / 你可以用它把矿石之类的原材料炼成更有用的东西。$u",
        "Sat2": "It's really satisfying when you can repair something yourself, instead of just throwing it away. / 东西坏掉了能自己修好，不用买新的，就很有成就感。",
        "FlowerDance_Accept": "Heh... sure! Suddenly, the dance sounds a lot more fun.$h / 欸……好啊！感觉舞会更加有意思了。$h",
        "Thu10": "Oh, @! Is there anything you want to talk to me about?$l / 噢，@！你是有事情要告诉我吗？$l",
        "Resort_Shore": "I wonder if Willy would let me bring my telescope here sometime...#The sky is so clear here, I bet I could spot Pelican Town out in the horizon.#Maybe I'd even see you running around %farm Farm! / 不知道威利以后会不会允许我把望远镜带过来……#这里的天空真是晴朗，我在地平线上肯定能看见鹈鹕镇。#说不定，我还能看到你在%farm农场里跑来跑去！",
        "AcceptGift_(O)336": "Ah, pure gold... It's not the strongest material, but it has some really useful properties!$h / 啊，纯金……这种材料并不是最坚硬的，不过有很多有用的性质！$h",
        "winter_1": "Oh man, it's so cold...$s / 唉唉，还真冷呢……$s",
        "Thu4": "Sometimes, when I'm looking into space with my telescope, I get struck with this eerie feeling... Like we aren't meant to see this. / 我用望远镜观察太空的时候，偶尔会突然有种诡异的感觉……这可能不是允许我们看到的东西。#$e#It's silly, I know...$h / 听起来很扯，是不是……$h",
        "Sat4": "Some people say 'magic isn't real'... but have they ever stopped and really thought about magnetism? / 有些人认为魔法全是假的……不知道他们有没有意识到存在磁场这么个东西？",
        "summer_Fri2": "Hey, tell me a story about farming. / 告诉我点耕种的趣事吧。#$e#That's really interesting! / 那可真有趣！",
        "summer_Sun": "I bet you're growing some interesting crops right now. / 你现在肯定在种些有趣的作物吧。#$b#Dad says a lot of exotic plants grow in the valley this time of year. / 老爸说，这时节山谷里会长出许多奇异的植物。",
        "AcceptGift_(O)910": "Ahh! Be careful with that! Are you touching it with your bare hands?$9 / 喂！小心点！你怎么可以直接用手拿？$9#$b#... Sorry... hehe... With proper handling, this will be perfect for an exotic machine I'm building. / ……不好意思……嘻嘻……我在造一台奇妙的机器，这个只要处理得当，就能排上大用场。",
        "fall_Sun": "Hey, here's to another good week! *toast* / 来，为完美的一周干杯吧！*干杯*",
        "winter_Thu": "Hey! What's up? / 嘿！最近怎么样？#$e#It's a good time to explore the caves. / 现在可是探索洞穴的好时机。#$e#I would go but my Dad would flip. / 我很想去，不过老爸一定会气死的。",
        "dating_Maru_memory_oneday": "Mmm... I'm having a hard time focusing on my work today.$l / 唔……我今天根本没法集中注意力干活。$l",
        "winter_Thu10": "@, come closer. I'm cold.$l / @，靠近一点嘛。我要冷死了。$l#$e#My hands are so dry from the winter air. I'm sorry about that.$l / 冬天太冷，我的手好像有些干燥。抱歉了。$l",
        "fall_Thu": "In other parts of the world it's spring right now. Imagine that! / 在世界的另一端，现在可是春天哦！想象一下吧！",
        "GreenRain_2": "This is a rare opportunity to study a unique phenomenon... every moment counts! / 难得有这么宝贵的机会可以研究罕见的现象……一点时间都不能浪费！",
        "Thu_01_02": "You're right, but I love a challenge!$h / 嗯，没错哦。不过我就喜欢知难而上！$h",
        "AcceptGift_(O)787": "This will be perfect for powering my latest project! Thanks, @!$h / 这个正好可以给我的新项目提供电力！谢谢你，@！$h",
        "winter_Wed": "I guess winter is a good time to work on my gadgets. / 冬日漫漫，正好用来加工我的小玩意儿。#$e#I wonder if I could make anything useful for farmers? / 不知道能不能造出些便于耕种的机械来呢？",
        "Tue2": "Stop by our house when you need to upgrade your buildings. / 如果你要升级你的建筑，就来我们家一趟吧。#$e#It's always nice to have visitors. / 我们总是很乐意接待访客。",
        "Resort": "I've been noticing a few different starfish species. My favorite are the big purple ones, but they're all very interesting! / 我发现了几种不同的海星。我最喜欢的是紫色的大海星，不过所有海星都非常有趣！",
        "Event_Hospital_3": "You're right. I should just tell him the truth.%fork$u / 你是对的。我应该告诉他真相。%fork$u",
        "Event_Cut1": "Oh no?$8 / 噢，真的吗？$8#$b#Well, that makes me feel a little better, then. Thanks. / 好吧，那我感觉好点了。谢谢你。",
        "eventSeen_9": "I should've spent more time on that piece before showing you...$s / 那个机器我应该多打磨一阵子再给你看的……$s",
        "event_robot2": "What? After she said point-blank that she doesn't want to be a slave? How cold...%fork$a / 什么？在她很明白地说过，不想做他人奴隶之后吗？真是冷漠……%fork$a",
        "summer_Mon6": "Come to my room if you ever want to tinker with my gadgets. / 如果你想要看我的小玩意儿，随时来我房间就行。",
        "fall_Thu10": "You have a leaf in your hair. Let me get it for you. / 你头上有片叶子哦。我来帮你取下来吧。#$e#...$h / ……$h",
        "winter_Sat2": "Hey, if any of your farming machines need to be fixed, just let me know.$h / 如果你农场上有什么东西要修，尽管叫我就行。$h",
        "event_robot_explain1": "...$s / ……$s#$b#You have a point, I did program her to act human... but her neural net is so complex, I can't be sure consciousness didn't emerge on its own.$8 / 你说得有道理，我的确编写了她的程序，想让她表现得更像人类……但她的脑神经反应网如此复杂，无法判定她的自我意识是不是通过自身形成的。$8#$b#Furthermore, isn't it a little arrogant to assume that human-like consciousness is the only worthwhile vessel of existence? Computer brains are different than ours, but that doesn't mean we can disregard them.$8 / 况且，难道只有人类的思维才配拥有自我意识吗？虽然机器人的大脑构造与我们截然不同，那也不代表我们就应该这样不尊重、不认可他们啊。$8",
        "summer_Wed2": "Is it just me or did it suddenly get really hot? / 感觉天气突然变热了，是我的错觉吗？#$e#I guess it's just me. / 大概是我的错觉吧。",
        "Wed8": "I'm glad to have a job at the clinic... I feel like I'm helping people in town. / 我周二和周四会去哈维的诊所上班。#$e#Dr. Harvey? He's nice, but not really my type... / 他人很好，但不是我喜欢的类型……",
        "event_robot1": "Thanks. That means a lot to me, @. / 谢谢你。这对我来说很重要，@。#$b#I know gadgets aren't really your kind of thing... but I do appreciate that you're showing interest in what I do. / 我知道你对这些小玩意儿不太在行……但我很感激你能对我所做的事感兴趣。#$b#I wish I could return the favor somehow.$l / 真希望我能通过什么方式报答你。$l",
        "winter_Tue": "My hair gets so frizzy in this dry weather. *sigh* / 天气干燥，连我的头发都枯燥起来了。*唉*",
        "winter_Tue4": "Hey, do you have any ideas for a new gadget I can make? / 给我出个点子，接下来该造怎样的新玩意儿呢？#$e#Mhmm. I trust your opinion. / 嗯嗯。我相信你的眼光。",
        "Sun": "Hi!#$q 3/4 Sun_01_old#Do you have fun working on the farm?#$r 3 0 Sun_01_01#Yes.#$r 4 0 Sun_01_02#No. / 嗨！#$q 3/4 Sun_01_old#你在农场工作得开心吗？#$r 3 0 Sun_01_01#开心。#$r 4 0 Sun_01_02#不开心。",
        "Thu_01_old": "See you later. / 回头见。",
        "AcceptGift_(O)122": "Ooh, this is exciting! I'll deconstruct it and see if I can reverse-engineer the technology.$h / 哇，这可太好了！我要把它拆开，看看能不能对里面的技术做逆向工程。$h",
        "married_Harvey": "You always seemed far too healthy to be at the clinic so often... Now it's all starting to make sense... / 我还在想，你身体这么好，为什么总是来诊所……原来是这样……",
        "divorced": "We have nothing to say to each other.$a / 我们之间没什么好说的。$a",
        "Fri6": "My Dad is very logical, and my Mom is very intuitive. That difference leads to conflict, sometimes...$s / 我爸很讲逻辑，而我妈总是凭直觉，所以有时候会吵架……$s",
        "Event_Space2": "I guess you could see it like that...$s / 也可以这么认为啦……$s#$b#But it's still incredible, isn't it? / 但还是很难以置信，对吧？",
        "summer_Fri": "I worked at the clinic yesterday. We didn't have a single patient. / 我昨天在医院上班。结果一个病人都没有。#$e#I guess people get sick less during summer. / 看来夏天大家身体都会比较健康呢。",
        "summer_Sun6": "Some day I'm going to be a world-class inventor.$u / 总有一天，我会成为世界闻名的发明家！$u#$e#You're lucky to be friends with me! / 到时候你就会觉得有我做朋友真好！#$b#...just kidding. / ……开个玩笑而已。",
        "Fri4": "My mother is a carpenter and my dad is a scientist. I guess it makes sense that I'm into building gadgets. / 我妈妈是个木匠，而我爸爸是个科学家。所以我爱组装些小玩意儿也不足为奇了吧。",
        "Tue": "Have you met my mother? She's the town's carpenter. / 你见过我母亲了吗？她是镇里的木匠。",
        "AcceptBirthdayGift_Negative": "Hey, what's this, a birthday gift? It's... uh, well, it's a gift! Thanks for remembering me, anyway. / 哇，这是给我的生日礼物吗？我……呃，那什么，我没说错！还是谢谢你记得我的生日。",
        "married_Penny": "Hey, congratulations!$h / 哎，恭喜你！$h#$b#I remember the first time Penny told me she had feelings for you... / 我还记得当时潘妮跟我说她喜欢你……#$b#She was all shy about it, but I knew right away it was serious... she wouldn't say something like that if she didn't mean it! / 她当时可害羞了，我立马就知道她是认真的……不然她可不会把那种话说出口！",
        "eventSeen_9_memory_oneweek": "How's your hand feeling? / 你的手怎么样了？#$b#Let me see it... Hey, it looks all better!$h / 我看看……哦，已经好多了！$h",
        "FlowerDance_Accept_Spouse": "Of course... *whisper* Then can we go home and snuggle?$l / 当然……*低声说*那么我们可以回家腻在一起了吗？$l",
        "summer_Wed": "Are you enjoying the season? / 你还喜欢最近的天气吧？#$e#It's been so warm this year.$h / 今年还真是暖和呢。$h",
        "Resort_Towel": "*gasp*... It's a solar eclipse!$3 / 嘶……是日食！$3#$b#Oh... never mind. It's just your body blocking the sun. / 噢……没事了。只是你的身子挡住了太阳而已。",
        "event_robot_explain3": "That's horrible! What's gotten into you, @?$a / 这话说得太无情了！你今天到底怎么回事，@？$a#$b#I'm just going to forget about this conversation... you aren't acting yourself.$a / 这次对话就当没发生过好了……你今天真是太不对劲了。$a",
        "summer_Mon": "Hmm... What sort of gadget should I tinker with this summer? / 嗯……今年夏天我搞点什么小玩意会比较好呢？",
        "event_robot3": "Heh...$8 / 呵……$8#$b#Yeah I guess he did kinda say that, didn't he?$l / 他似乎的确说过这种话呢？$l#$b#...Um...$l / ……呃……$l",
        "fall_Fri": "I bet we'll start seeing more people at the clinic this season.$s / 这个季节诊所的病人应该也会多起来吧。$s#$e#I hope everyone stays healthy. / 希望大家能保重身体呢。",
        "summer_Tue8": "@, you're looking sharp today.$h / @，你今天看起来挺不错哦。$h",
        "Thu_0": "Really? Are you sure you're not just trying to flatter me? / 真的？你不是在恭维我吧？",
        "Event_Hospital_2": "Okay. I'll blame it on you, then.$u / 好。那我就全怪你了。$u",
        "Sat": "Do you know my Dad, Demetrius? He's a scientist. I have a lot of fun helping him out in the laboratory. / 你认识我爸爸德米特里厄斯吗？他是个科学家。在实验室里帮他做研究很有趣呢。",
        "Event_Hospital_1": "Of course he'll know the difference! This sample is completely ruined!%fork$s / 他肯定能看出差别！这个样品全毁了！%fork$s",
        "Sun_01_old": "$p 3#Hey, you've made another week of progress on the farm! It seems like things are going well for you.$h / 嘿，你又在农场上工作了一周！看起来你过得还不错。$h|Another tiring week on the farm, huh? It must really be a lot of work...$s / 这周的农活一定很累吧？肯定有不少活要干……$s",
        "Thu_01_01": "You don't think I could do it?$s / 你是觉得我做不到吗？$s",
        "winter_Mon": "Did you see the snowman I built?$h / 你看没看见我堆的那个雪人？$h",
        "dating_Maru": "Ummm... Don't break the news to my Dad, okay? I'll handle it. / 呃……你别去跟我爸说，好吗？我会处理的。",
        "Fri": "Hey, sorry if I seem cranky... I'm a little sore from work yesterday.#$c .5# I had to carry ten boxes of medical files to the attic! / 嘿，很抱歉我有点暴躁……因为昨天的工作，我现在浑身酸痛。#$c .5#我得把十箱医疗档案全都搬到阁楼里去！#$e#I had to sort patient records for four hours straight!  / 然后又花了整整四个小时分类整理病历！ ",
        "Resort_Leaving": "That was fun! / 真有趣！",
        "Event_Cut2": "Oh no! Aghh... I'm really really sorry.$s / 噢，不！啊……我十分抱歉。$s",
        "married_Sebastian": "Hey, I guess we're brother and sister now!$h / 哎，你现在也算是我哥了！$h^Hey, I guess we're sisters now!$h / 哎，你现在是我嫂子啦！$h#$e#I'm glad that Sebastian found a way out of the basement... / 塞巴斯蒂安终于能离开地下室，我很高兴……#$e#I wish you two all the best! / 祝你们一帆风顺！",
        "Resort_Bar": "Mmmm... Why are tropical fruits so good? / 嗯嗯……为什么热带水果这么好吃？",
        "fall_Fri6": "I've been feeling especially optimistic lately...$h / 我最近啊……觉得特别乐观呢。$h",
        "event_robot4": "...$8 / ……$8#$b#@...$8 / @……$8"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/Mister Qi",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "QiNutRoom_Mon": "There's more to this world than meets the eye, kid. Some day, you might understand. / 孩子，世界并不只有视力所及的范围。总有一天，你会明白的。#$b#For now, just keep striving for excellence in everything you do. / 现在，你只要在做每一件事情时精益求精就好。",
        "QiNutRoom_Tue": "I got to where I am through the force of pure willpower, kid. / 孩子，我是通过纯粹的意志力来到我所处的位置的。#$b#You see... The mind is a very powerful tool. / 你看……头脑是一件十分强大的工具。#$b#In fact, it's the most powerful tool in all of reality... and beyond. / 事实上，它是整个现实世界中最为强大的工具……甚至不仅仅止于现实世界。",
        "Sun": "Keep working hard and maybe you'll end up like me someday. / 继续努力，总有一天你也会像我一样。",
        "QiNutRoom_Fri": "Set your eyes on the furthest star, and let that be your goal. / 将你的目光落在最遥远的星星上，然后把它当作你的目标。#$b#It's always within your power to go one step further than you used to believe. / 你总是能够百尺竿头更进一步，超出你原本以为的极限。",
        "Wed": "I was born an ordinary boy, but I made a decision early in life that I would become extraordinary. / 我出生时也只是个普通的男孩子。但我从小就下定主意，要变得更加出色。",
        "Thu": "Hey. Don't tell anyone about this place, okay? I want to keep it... exclusive. / 嘿。你可不要到处跑来跑去，宣扬这个地方，知道吗？这里可是我的……秘密基地呢。#$e#You'd keep a secret for your friend Mr. Qi, wouldn't you? / 就请你为了我，保守这个秘密吧？",
        "Tue": "I knew you'd end up here someday. Of course, I had to make it a little difficult so you'd have an incentive to achieve excellence. / 我就知道你总有一天会到这里。当然，为了能让你更加努力，我稍微提升了一点难度。",
        "QiNutRoom_Wed": "I'm impressed with your tenacity, kid... it took a lot of walnuts to get this far. / 我惊讶于你的顽强，孩子……想要到这里可是需要很多核桃的。",
        "QiNutRoom_Thu": "Wherever you go... I'm always behind the curtain, making sure the show is interesting. Hahaha... / 无论你走到哪……我总会在帷幕之后，确保好戏在上演。哈哈哈……#$b#Or... am I? / 不过……是这样吗？",
        "QiNutRoom_Sat": "Some things transcend time and space, kid. It's a unique feeling in the heart... a whisper of things beyond. / 有些东西超越了时间与空间，孩子。这是内心深处的一种独特感受……是来自遥远之物的低语。",
        "Sat": "Stop by whenever you wanna relax. / 想要放松的时候，就来这里吧。",
        "QiNutRoom_Sun": "On the left, you'll find a board with my special challenges... custom-tailored for you, kid. / 在左边，你能找到一块板子，上面有我的特殊挑战……是专门为你量身订制的，孩子。#$b#On the right, a set of fantastic prizes for those who meet my challenge... / 在右边，有很多奖赏，专门留给那些完成挑战的人……#$b#Good luck, kid. / 祝你好运，孩子。",
        "Mon": "Keep it up, kid. I think you're gonna be a star. / 继续努力，孩子。你一定会功成名就的。#$e#Just ask me if you need anything. / 需要什么东西的话，只管告诉我就是了。",
        "Fri": "Never stop striving to achieve perfection. / 永远不要放弃努力。#$e#Settle for nothing less than excellence in everything you do. / 做什么事情都要做到尽善尽美。",
        "married": "That was a very auspicious wedding ceremony, @. / @，你的婚礼办得非常吉利。#$b#...What? You didn't see me there? / ……你说什么？没看到我？#$b#Hahaha... Kid... You can't keep a secret from Mr. Qi. / 哈哈哈……年轻人……齐先生可是无所不知、无所不晓。"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/Pam",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "Saloon_Wed": "*Sigh*... Hey, kid. You're too young to be moping around in a place like this. / *唉* ……喂，小子，你这样的年轻人不该在这里逛游。",
        "summer_Tue2": "Oh, it's Mr. @. / 哦，这位是@先生。^Oh it's Miss @. / 哦，这位是@小姐。#$e#Do you need my help or something? / 需要我帮你做些什么吗？",
        "event_credit2": "...it isn't? That's terrible!$s / ……不是吗？那太糟糕了！$s#$b#...Oh.$s / ……呃$s",
        "Thu": "#$1 PamDrunk#Blahh... I had one too many caramel porters at the saloon last night... Go away. / 唉唉……昨晚稍微喝多了些，现在不舒服……快走开。$k#$e#My house ain't pretty but at least it's by the river. / 虽然我这房子不怎么样，但至少就在河边。#$e#Hey. Penny's my baby girl. Be nice to her or leave her alone, got it? / 嘿。潘妮可是我的宝贝女儿，你别欺负她，知道了吗？",
        "summer_Thu": "Oh, hi there, farmer. / 你好啊，农夫。#$e#I don't often chit-chat with strangers. / 我不太习惯和陌生人讲话。",
        "fall_Tue": "If I knew you better, I'd be more inclined to chat. / 如果和你更熟的话，可能会更谈的开吧。",
        "Introduction": "Hey, kid. The name's Pam. / 你好，孩子。我叫潘姆。#$e#Don't be a jerk and we'll get along fine. / 只要你态度不恶劣，我们一定会成为朋友的。",
        "Saloon_Sun": "%Pam seems out of it. Better leave her alone right now. / %潘姆似乎睡过去了。还是不要打扰她吧。",
        "summer_Sat": "Someone's been complainin' about my yard... sayin' it's a mess. Was it you?$u / 有人在到处抱怨我的院子太乱。是你吗？$u#$e#Hmmm... / 嗯……",
        "Mon": "#$1 PamDrank#Urghh... my head... / 噢……我的头……$k#$e#You know, I'd eat healthier food if I could afford it. / 如果有钱的话，谁不想吃得健康点啊。#$e#Hey, you probably have a lot of tasty grub growin' on your farm, hm? / 喂，你那农场上一定种了不少好吃的，对吧？",
        "summer_Thu4": "I always seem to end up at the saloon at some point. / 我总是不知不觉得就跑到酒吧坐坐。#$e#It's too close to my house. It ain't healthy. / 大概是离我家太近了吧。这生活方式太不健康。",
        "MovieInvitation": "Date night with ol' Pam, huh? Hah!$h / 跟老潘姆的约会之夜吗？哈！$h^Ladies night with ol' Pam, huh? Hah!$h / 跟老潘姆的闺蜜之夜吗？哈！$h#$b#Sure thing, kid... I'll see you there. / 当然好啊，孩子……我们到时候见。",
        "cc_Bus": "Hey, did you hear about the ol' bus? / 嘿，你听说过那辆老巴士吗？#$b#Yep... I'm back on the saddle, kid... hehe. Feels nice.$h / 听说过……我又坐上驾驶座了，孩子……嘿嘿。感觉不错。$h",
        "fall_Wed": "*Sigh*... I guess I'll be popping a frozen dinner into the microwave tonight.$s / *唉*……看来今天的晚餐又要吃速冻食品了。$s",
        "Saloon_Entry": "Ah... Finally./I need a drink./Gus! Gimme the usual./Hey, I'm back!/Ooh boy, am I thirsty!/I'm parched! / 啊……终于能歇会了。/得赶紧喝一杯。/格斯！就来我平常那杯。/喂！我回来了！/啊啊，还真是喉咙冒烟了！/简直要渴死了！",
        "Fri2": "You know, I've been thinking... I wish I had a hobby. Something to do other than hanging around at that saloon every night. / 其实，我一直在想……要是自己有个什么爱好就好了。这样也就不会每天晚上都去酒吧鬼混。#$e#You got any ideas? / 你有没有什么好主意？#$e#...Ehh. Maybe I'll play checkers against myself. / ……唔，要么我自己和自己下五子棋怎么样？",
        "Wed": "$d bus#You don't know how glad I am that the bus is up and running! I feel alive again. / 这巴士重新开始运行，我真是再高兴不过了！感觉整个人又活了过来。|Times have been tough lately. I got laid off of my job as a bus driver. If I got that job back I could drive you to Calico Desert. / 最近我过得不太好。前几天被公司给辞了，丢了巴士司机的工作。如果能重新当回巴士司机，就能载你去卡利科沙漠了。",
        "Trailer_Entry": "Penny! Did you make dinner?/Penny! You done your chores?/Penny! You home?/Hey! I'm home! / 潘妮！做完饭了吗？/潘妮！家务干了吗？/潘妮！你在家吗？/喂！我回来了！",
        "structureBuilt_Fish Pond": "Heard you got a fish pond built... Heh, I grew up with a fish pond. / 听说你建了一个鱼塘……嚯，我可是在鱼塘旁边长大的。#$b#You can raise just about anything in one of those... But some of the fancier fish are real fussy! / 几乎什么鱼都可以养在里面……但是有些稀有的鱼挑剔得很！",
        "fall_Sat": "Would you do me a kindness and clean up my house? / 你能不能帮帮忙，打扫一下我家？#$e#Just kidding.$h / 说笑呢。$h",
        "Resort_Chair": "Now this is comfort! I might even take my shoes off!$h / 真是舒服啊！我想把鞋子也脱掉！$h#$e#Better not look too closely at my feet, kid. / 孩子，最好别凑近了看我的脚。",
        "pamHouseUpgrade": "I can't believe you bought me a house! Is there any catch? / 不敢相信，你给我买了房子！有什么陷井吗？#$e#Sorry, I'm not used to people being so nice...$s / 对不起，我还不习惯人们对我这么好……$s",
        "fall_Sun4": "I miss my old truck driving job. I used to go all around the valley, meetin' people, listenin' to the radio. / 真想念以前当卡车司机的时候。以前我开着大卡到处跑，能见到各种各样的人，还能天天听广播。#$e#Times sure do change. / 人生真是说变就变呢。",
        "Saloon_Fri": "Oi, Gus! Gimme another pint of your strongest! / 格斯！最烈的酒再给我来一杯！",
        "winter_Fri": "Penny sure does like old books. I think she's a heck of a lot smarter than I ever was. / 潘妮还真是喜欢旧书。我小时候脑子可没她那么聪明。#$e#I'm glad. / 我很欣慰。",
        "winter_Tue4_inlaw_Penny": "Hey. You better be treatin' Penny right on that old farm of yours. She's the only one I got! / 喂。你在农场里一定要好好对待潘妮。我就只剩她一个人了！",
        "winter_Sun": "Blah... my front yard's a mess.$s / 啊啊……我的前院还真乱。$s",
        "GreenRain": "It's a sign from the Almighty... We're doomed...%noturn$s / 这是上帝的信号……我们要完蛋了……%noturn$s",
        "AcceptGift_(O)StardropTea": "Well I'll be darned... I never expected to get a gift like this. You made my day, kid! / 我滴个乖乖……我没想到会收到这样的礼物。孩子，我很高兴！",
        "summer_Wed4": "Maybe if you do real well on your farm it'll boost the local economy. / 如果你的农场景气的话，或许当地的经济也会好转。#$e#Then everyone will have a job and we'll all be happy, right? / 然后大家就都有工作了，然后就皆大欢喜了不是吗？",
        "summer_Tue": "Hi, stranger. / 你好啊，陌生人。",
        "winter_Sat": "I oughta take up fishin', seein' as how close the river is. / 河就在眼前，我是不是该学学钓鱼……",
        "Resort_Shore": "Looks like there's some unique fish swimmin' around. Next time I'll have to bring my pole! / 看来周围有不少罕见的鱼，下次我必须得把鱼竿带上！",
        "reject_867": "Wow, would you look at that... It's like something out of the future. / 哇哦，看看这个……像是来自未来的东西。#$b#Hehe, sorry kid... I can't use that. There's more buttons than I have brain cells!$h / 哈哈，抱歉了孩子……我用不来这个。这上面的按钮甚至比我的脑细胞还多！$h",
        "Thu4": "Penny says I spend too much time at the saloon...$s / 潘妮说我在酒吧待的时间太久了……$s",
        "Sat4": "I wish a team of elves would come during the night and tidy up my house. Hahahaha.$h / 如果每天晚上有些小妖精出来替我打扫房间就好了。哈哈哈。$h#$e#I could sure go for some parsnips. / 还真想吃些防风草呢。#$e#If my legs weren't so stiff I'd visit the mountains every now and then. / 如果我的腿没事的话，偶尔也想去山里看看呢。",
        "fall_Sun": "Don't you have work to do? / 你没活干吗？#$e#You should be thankful that you have a job rather than moping around town all the time. / 有工作就知足吧，至少不用每天在镇上游荡。",
        "winter_Thu": "It's awful cold. A visit to the saloon should warm me up, don't you think? Heh heh. / 今天还真是冷。或许去酒吧一趟，喝几杯就暖和了。呵呵。#$e#Why don't you swing by the saloon later for a taste o' the Oh-Be-Joyful? / 不如你晚上也来酒吧坐坐，和我一起喝两杯？",
        "fall_Tue4": "I used to be young, once. Hard to believe, huh? / 别看我现在这样，很久以前我也像你这么年轻呢。#$e#Time sure goes fast when you grow up.$s / 人老了，感觉时间也过得飞快。$s",
        "Saloon_Sat": "%Pam isn't responding. / %潘姆没有任何反应。",
        "fall_Thu": "Penny's the only one I've got, so you best treat her kindly. / 我除了潘妮一无所有。你可要好好待她。",
        "GreenRain_2": "I think these rains are a show of force... a warning. / 我觉得这场雨是在宣示力量……是一种告诫。#$b#You could say it's from nature, from Yoba, whatever you like... but that's what I think. / 至于是来自大自然还是来自由巴，这就随便你怎么想了……反正我觉得是这样。#$e#What I mean is, we can't get too cocky. Or else, instead of a green rain, maybe we'll have a blood-red rain... See what I mean? / 说白了就是咱们不能太狂妄，不然下的可能不是绿雨而是血雨了……懂我意思不？",
        "Saloon_Tue": "Hey Gus! Gimme another round! *hic*$h / 喂，格斯！再来一杯！*打嗝*$h",
        "winter_Wed": "Hey kid. What're you up to? / 喂，孩子！你这是要去干什么？#$e#I'm just passin' time, same as always. / 我只是和平常一样，消磨时间而已。",
        "divorced_Penny": "Penny came home crying... what'd you do to her?$3 / 潘妮哭着回家了……你对她做了什么？$3",
        "Resort": "Heh... Willy gave us each a piece of his fish jerky on the ride over. Delicious! / 啊……在路上，威利给每个人分了一块鱼干，非常美味！",
        "Tue2": "I was reading the newspaper this morning but then I got depressed. It's a rotten world, kid. / 我今天早上本来是在读报纸的，结果搞得很郁闷。这世界简直是烂透了。#$e#Keep your head screwed on right and you'll make it through in one piece... / 你也得当心啊，不然早晚会搞得头破血流……#$b#That's what my Pappy always used to say. Heh heh heh.$h / 我老爸以前一直对我这么说。呵呵。$h",
        "summer_Tue6": "I had hopes and dreams like you, once... But look at me now.$s / 我以前也像你一样，有梦想也有希望……现在还不是落得这个下场。$s#$e#Life doesn't always turn out like you expect. / 生活总是不尽人意。#$e#Ah well. There's no sense dwellin' on what you don't have. / 不过话说回来，在这里自怨自艾也不是办法。",
        "pamHouseUpgrade_memory_oneweek": "I'm loving the new house. Thanks again, kid!$h / 我很喜欢新房子，孩子，真心谢谢你啊！$h",
        "Saloon6": "Hey, kid. I'd buy you a drink if I could afford it! / 你好，孩子。如果我有钱的话，一定请你喝一杯！",
        "winter_Tue": "Do you want somethin' from me, kid? Best look somewhere else. / 你找我是想要点什么吗？还是去别处吧。",
        "winter_Tue4": "I just hope Penny has a good life ahead of her. If you ever have kids you'll know how I feel. / 我就是想让潘妮以后有好日子过。等你有了自己的孩子，就明白我的心情了。#$e#...It's so dry in winter. My skin feels like old parchment. / ……冬天还真是干燥。感觉皮肤都皱成了羊皮纸。",
        "GreenRainFinished": "Well, I guess the end-times haven't come just yet, kid... / 哎，大概末日还没到吧，孩子……#$e#Ah well, back to the ol' nine to five... / 唉，继续朝九晚五吧……",
        "Sun": "Are you friends with Gus? He's a pretty good guy. / 你和格斯是朋友吗？他这人挺不错的。#$e#He even gives me free beer on my birthday. / 我生日的时候，他还给我免费啤酒来着。",
        "married_Alex": "So, you married the Mullner boy, huh? / 所以你真的跟莫尔纳家的小伙子结婚了？#$b#Will you be takin' that smelly old dog with ya, too? / 那条臭烘烘的老狗你也带过去吗？",
        "wonIceFishing": "Alright, alright... you beat me fair and square at the fishing event, kid. / 好吧……孩子，钓鱼比赛你确实堂堂正正赢了我。#$e#Hmm... maybe my problem was using that beer-battered mushroom as bait...$u / 唔……我可能不应该用啤酒面糊炸蘑菇当鱼饵……$u",
        "summer_Fri": "...Yeah? / ……是吗？#$e#You're a fine lookin' young man. Why're you wastin' your time talkin' to an old girl like me? / 你这小伙子年轻英俊，干嘛要来和我这老女人搭讪？^You're a pretty gal. What're you wastin' your time talkin' to someone like me for? / 你这么年轻貌美，为什么要来特意和我说话？",
        "Tue": "Hey, you! Don't be snoopin' around the trailer when I'm out. Got it?$u / 喂！你可不要趁我不在偷偷溜进我的房车！懂了吗？$u#$e#Sorry, but I gotta be cautious with strangers. / 不好意思，只是不太信得过陌生人而已。",
        "Saloon": "Nothin' like a sip o' the good stuff to warm these old bones...$h / 我这把老骨头，就靠喝点小酒才能暖和过来……$h",
        "married_Penny": "I'll really miss that girl...$s / 我很想念我的女儿……$s#$b#You treat my Penny good, now. You hear me?$u / 你对我家潘妮要好好的，听到没有？$u",
        "summer_Wed": "Havin' a local farm is good for our town. / 当地拥有一座农场对小镇来说可是件好事。",
        "Thu4_inlaw_Penny": "It's awful lonely at home all by myself... / 一个人在拖车里面简直孤独得可怕……",
        "Saloon_Thu": "*gulp* ... I've been looking forward to this beverage all afternoon. Heh heh. / *大口喝酒*……一下午就盼着能来这里喝一口了。呵呵。",
        "fall_Fri": "Every day is the same old routine...$s / 每天都是一成不变……$s#$e#Do you ever have that problem, farmer? / 你有没有这么觉得呢，农夫？",
        "event_credit1": "Hey, watch your mouth! No one tells me what to do!$u / 喂，说话时注意点！不用你来告诉我该干什么不该干什么！$u",
        "pamHouseUpgradeAnonymous": "I can't believe someone bought me a house! I wonder if it's some kind of scam? / 我不敢相信有人给我买了房子！我想知道这是不是某种骗局？#$e#Sorry, I'm not used to people being so nice...$s / 对不起，我还不习惯人们对我这么好……$s",
        "Sat": "Make sure your boots are clean before you go stompin' around in my house.$u / 进来之前，你最好在门口把鞋上的泥都擦干净。$u#$e#It's annoying to clean a mess. You should know that by now. / 擦地板实在是太麻烦了。你也应该体谅一下。",
        "summer_Sat2": "Don't mind that ol' dog next to the house. / 别怕附近那条狗。#$b#He might look at you cross, but he'll never get up from that box in a hunderd years. / 虽然看起来可能有点凶，不过那狗是不会冲过来咬你的。#$b#The old boy's name? It's Dusty. / 你想知道那狗叫什么？就叫达斯迪啊。",
        "winter_Mon": "You got any hogs on that farm? / 你的农场有没有野猪？",
        "Fri": "Each day's just the same as the last...$s / 每天都是这么的单调，简直无聊透顶……$s#$b#If only I'd been born rich...$s / 如果出生在有钱人家就好了……$s",
        "Resort_Bar": "It's a special occasion, kid... I'm ordering something unique. Make it a double!$h / 孩子，情况特殊……我要点一杯特别的。要烈一点的！$h"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/Penny",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "Fri8": "I shouldn't complain so much about chores... some people in the world are really struggling, and here I am complaining about doing dishes...$s / 我不该整天因为做家务而发牢骚……世界上还有人在水深火热之中，我却在这抱怨洗碗的事情……$s",
        "fall_Sat8": "Hi @.$h / 嗨，@。$h#$e#Your farmhouse must be pretty easy to clean, huh? / 你的农舍应该很容易清扫吧？",
        "Resort_Entering": "This island is so beautiful! / 这座岛真是太漂亮了！",
        "Resort_Towel_2": "I'm reading a book about a sailor who washes up on a deserted island. / 我在读一本书，讲的是一名水手流落到荒岛上的故事。#$b#I wonder what I would do in that sort of a situation? / 我在想如果我处在那样的情况下，会怎么做呢？",
        "Thu": "We're very lucky to have a library in such a small town. / 这么小的镇上还建了图书馆，我们真是十分幸运。#$e#When you're lost in a book, it's easy to forget the realities of your life.$u / 当你沉浸在书中的世界时，很容易就忘记了现实的平凡与喧嚣。$u#$e#...Maybe that's why I like reading so much.$s / ……或许这就是我喜爱读书的理由吧。$s#$e#...Sorry. I got carried away there. / ……抱歉。是不是有点啰嗦了呢。",
        "Thu6": "I wish I could keep a garden, but our yard is such a mess.$u / 如果能开个小花园就好了，不过我们的前院实在是太脏了。$u#$e#Maybe I'll live in a place where I can have a garden someday. / 或许有一天，我也能住在有花园的地方。#$e#Maybe I'll live on a farm! *giggle*$h / 也许我会住在农场呢！* 咯咯笑 *$h",
        "Resort_Shore_2": "Somehow, the water here looks so different... / 这里的水看起来有点不一样……#$e#I can hardly believe this is the same ocean I've been gazing at my entire life. / 我很难相信，这里和我注视了一辈子的海水竟然属于同一片大洋。",
        "Introduction": "Oh... Hello! I'm Penny... / 哦……你好！我是潘妮……",
        "event_pool5": "Y...You don't?$8 / 你……你竟然？ $8#$b#...!!!%fork$10 / ……！！！%fork$10",
        "summer_Sat": "Hello. Ummm...$u / 你好。唔唔……$u#$b#The mountains look nice today, don't they?$u / 今天的山色十分秀丽，对吧？$u",
        "Mon": "Hi...  / 你好……#$e#Oh, did you want something? / 怎么，有什么事吗？",
        "event_speaker_kids6": "Oh...$s / 噢……$s#$b#That's kind of sad... but I guess I can understand your point.$s / 虽然有些令人伤感，但我也不是不能理解你的观点。$s",
        "secondChance_Girls": "You've left a permanent scar on my heart, @. Still... I'm ready to speak to you again.$s / 你在我的心上留下了永久的伤疤，@。然而……我准备好再次和你说话。$s",
        "Mon_8": "Maybe you're right. It's better to cope with reality.$u / 或许你说得对。还是接受现实比较好。$u",
        "summer_Mon4": "$d cc#Thanks for fixing the community center back up. I guess you're kind of a town hero. / 感谢你把社区活动中心重建起来。这下你可算是小镇的英雄了呢。|Hello, @. It's nice to see you're doing well. / 您好，@。看来你最近过得不错哦。",
        "Wed2": "You know what? I should take the children on a field trip some time. Maybe to the forest. / 对了！我觉得应该带孩子去野外郊游。干脆去森林好了。#$e#A guest speaker would be nice... maybe someone familiar with nature? / 最好再请一个特邀讲师……找一个熟悉自然的人如何？#$e#Sorry, I'm just thinking out loud. / 抱歉，我只是在自言自语而已。",
        "FlowerDance_Decline": "Oh... No, thanks.$s / 噢……不用了，谢谢。$s",
        "dating_Penny_memory_oneweek": "I'm trying to finish this book, but I keep getting distracted thinking of you.$l / 我想看完这本书，可我总是分心想起你。$l",
        "dating_Penny_memory_oneday": "Suddenly, the world looks a lot more beautiful, don't you think? / 我感觉世界突然明亮了，你呢？",
        "event_speaker_kids1": "Oh no?$l / 噢，不是吧？$l#$b#Well, I guess that makes sense... you're busy with other things right now. / 唔，这也没办法呢……你现在应该还忙着别的事情吧。",
        "Wed": "We don't have a school here but I'm doing my best to give Vincent and Jas a proper education. / 虽然镇里没有学校，但我一直都在努力，想要好好教导文森特与贾斯。#$e#Every child deserves a chance to be successful. / 每个孩子都应该有成功的机会才对。#$e#Jas is very good at math and reading. Vincent is good at... well, he has an active imagination! / 贾斯的数学和阅读理解都很不错。文森特他……唔，他的想象力很丰富哦！",
        "dumped_Girls": "I can't bear to see you...$s / 我无法忍受再见到你……$s",
        "AcceptBirthdayGift_Positive": "For my birthday? That's so nice of you! It's a great gift.$h / 给我的生日礼物吗？你对我真好！我很喜欢。$h",
        "pamHouseUpgrade": "What you did for my family is so generous. Thank you! / 你为我的家人所做的事是如此慷慨。谢谢你！",
        "event_cook1": "You really mean it? Thank you! ... it's such a relief to hear that.$h / 你真的这么认为吗？谢谢你！……听到你这么说我就松了一口气呢。$h#$b#I've been working so hard on this recipe, and I'm really proud of it. / 毕竟是我花了心思制作出来的，我自己是很引以为豪啦。",
        "event_family3": "I see.$s / 原来是这样。$s",
        "eventSeen_35_memory_oneweek": "$y '@, what do you think... should a person be judged by their actions, or by their intentions?_Actions_Hmm... but don't we all make mistakes sometimes?$s_Intentions_Mmhmm... But what if you intend to do good, yet your actions cause harm?$s_Both_That's true... I guess it doesn't have to be one or the other. It might depend on the situation, too.' / $y '@，你觉得……一个人，应该看他的做法，还是看他的想法？_做法_唔……但是人做事情难免会犯错吧？$s_想法_唔……但万一你的想法是好的，做法却伤害到别人了呢？$s_都要看_确实……也许不一定要非此即彼，有时候还是要综合具体情况考虑。'#$b#I was just wondering what you thought... / 只是问问你的看法，没别的意思……",
        "winter_Fri": "...yes?$u / ……怎么了？$u",
        "event_pool1": "That's right...$8 / 没错……$8",
        "GreenRain": "Are you alright? We're all wondering what's going on...$3 / 你没事吧？我们都搞不清楚发生什么了……$3",
        "fall_Mon": "Hi... Um, are you doing okay?$u / 你好……嗯，今天你还好吗？$u",
        "breakUp": "...$s / ……$s#$b#I... I see... *sniff* ... W... We can just be friends, then.$s / 我……我知道了……（抽鼻子）……那……那我们就做朋友吧。$s",
        "AcceptGift_(O)StardropTea": "Mmm... it's so fragrant. I'm going to love this. / 嗯……好香啊，我很喜欢。",
        "Tue4": "$d bus#Maybe now that my mother has her bus driving job back, I can start saving more money. Things are looking a little brighter. / 不过如果妈妈能重新当回巴士司机的话，我们就能存更多的钱了。嗯，未来也稍微光明了一些呢。|I'm trying to save money from my tutoring job, but it's hard with my mother out of work. / 我当家教的钱本来是想存起来的，可妈妈没有工作，很难存钱。$s",
        "event_old4": "That's a horrible thing to say. Life is a precious thing to waste like that!$a / 你说得太过分了！生命如此珍贵，怎么可以随便浪费！$a",
        "eventSeen_34_memory_oneweek": "I've been teaching Jas and Vincent about Dwarvish Archaeology... / 我平时在给贾斯和文森特讲矮人考古学……#$b#Jas is curious about the origins of the Dwarves... but Vincent is mainly interested in dwarvish weapons!$h / 贾斯对矮人的起源很好奇……文森特倒是对矮人武器感兴趣！$h",
        "Sat2": "$d Joja#Things changed a lot after the JojaMart went up. It's been really bad for Pierre's shop. Mom loves JojaMart, though. The prices are cheap, so she can afford a lot more there than she ever could at Pierre's. / Joja 超市开了之后，镇上的事情都不一样了。皮埃尔的商店现在很不景气。不过妈妈特别喜欢 Joja。比起皮埃尔商店，在那里可以买到很多很便宜的东西。|Mom's been complaining ever since JojaMart closed down. I think it's good for her, though. Maybe she'll drink less Joja Cola now. / 自从 Joja 停业之后，妈妈就一直在抱怨。不过我觉得这样对她也好。或许她现在不会天天喝 Joja 可乐了。",
        "event_mail2": "Oh... I guess you're right.$l / 哦……也许你说得对。$l#$b#I'm sorry, Mr. Mullner. It was rude, what I did.$s / 抱歉，莫尔纳先生。我之前的行为十分没有礼貌。$s",
        "FlowerDance_Accept": "Oh... with me? Yes, of course!$h / 欸……跟我吗？当然可以啊！$h#$b#...Will you take the lead, though? I'm nervous...$12 / ……那个，你能不能带着我一点？我有点紧张……$12",
        "Resort_Shore": "I'm a little embarrassed wearing my bathing suit in public.$s / 当众穿着泳衣感觉有点不好意思。$s#$b#I hope no one's looking...$s / 我希望没人在看……$s",
        "event_pool3": "No!$9 / 不！$9",
        "summer_Sun": "So... do you like to decorate your farm house? / 那么……你喜欢装饰自己的农舍吗？#$e#It must be nice having your own place to decorate. / 有自己的房间可以装饰，一定很开心吧。",
        "eventSeen_34_memory_twoweeks": "Vincent has been asking me about slugs for weeks... so I prepared a whole lesson on them. They're actually pretty interesting! / 文森特这几个星期一直在问我鼻涕虫的问题……所以我准备给他们上一节关于鼻涕虫的课。鼻涕虫还挺有趣的！#$e#Whenever I see a banana slug, I feel like it's a sign of good luck. / 每次看到香蕉鼻涕虫的时候，我就感觉要走好运了。",
        "Tue10": "Um, @? A farm seems like a good place for children, don't you think?$l / 呃，@？如果要养小孩的话，农场是个不错的地方，你觉得呢？$l#$e#It was just a thought I had.$l / 我也只是随便想想啦。$l",
        "winter_Thu": "Oh... hi. You want to talk?$u / 噢……嗨。你想聊聊是吗？$u#$e#If you find any interesting artifacts or minerals, Gunther will gladly display them in the museum. / 如果找到了新奇的古物或者矿物，都可以拿给冈瑟看看，放到博物馆里进行展览。#$e#He told me he has special gifts for people who donate. / 他之前说过，如果有人进行捐赠，会有特别的小礼物相赠哦。",
        "dating_Maru_memory_oneday": "Hi, @. Maru told me the news... I'm happy for you two!$h / 哎，@，玛鲁跟我说了……你们俩在一起我很开心！$h",
        "fall_Tue4": "Your farm looks really pretty right now.$h / 你的农场现在看起来好美哦。$h",
        "AcceptBirthdayGift_Loved": "Oh! Is this for me? For... for my birthday?$3 / 啊！这是给我的吗？算是……生日礼物？$3#$b#*sniff*... Sorry.$s / （吸鼻子）……抱歉。$s#$b#I'm... just not used to such kindness... / 我就是有点……没习惯别人对我这么好。#$b#... I love it, though. It's perfect. Thank you so much. / ……呃，我超喜欢这个，真的。非常感谢你。",
        "event_speaker_kids3": "Yes... the urge to care for something innocent and helpless. It makes sense that we'd feel that. / 嗯……希望保护弱小无辜之物的情感。我们这么想也是理所应当的。",
        "GreenRain_2": "This strange weather is a good opportunity to get the kids interested in nature!$h / 这种奇怪的天气可以让孩子们对大自然产生兴趣！$h",
        "event_cook2": "Oh... Uh, sure.$s / 噢……呃，那好吧。$s",
        "event_pool4": "...Oh, @. I thought you did, but I wasn't sure.$6 / ……哦，@。我还以为你早就意识到了，只是不确定而已。$6#$b#...I'll always remember this night.$6 / ……今天晚上将会是我一生的回忆。$6^You look so beautiful tonight... I... *gasp*$6 / 你今晚看起来真的很美……我……* 喘气 *$6",
        "Resort": "This sand is so soft and fine. It feels great on my toes!$h / 这里的沙子真是柔软又细腻。脚趾上的触感真好！$h",
        "event_old1": "I guess you're right... why stress out about something you can't change?$u / 你说得也有道理……不能改变的事情，就不要这么纠结了。$u",
        "event_speaker_kids5": "hmm...$s / 嗯……$s#$b#If everyone thought like that, humans would die out.$s / 如果大家都这么想的话，估计人类也要灭绝了吧。$s",
        "winter_Tue": "I try to stay indoors as much as possible during the winter. I hate being cold. / 冬天的时候还是待在屋里比较好。最讨厌天寒地冻的了。",
        "winter_Tue4": "I'm looking forward to seeing what your farm looks like in the spring. / 好期待进入春天后农场的景色啊。#$e#It's going to be so fresh and beautiful.$h / 一定会是万物复苏的美景吧。$h",
        "Resort_Towel_2_Married": "Hey honey, do you mind standing a little to the left? / 亲爱的，你可以稍微往左边站一点吗？#$b#Thanks, the sun was making it a little bit hard to read!$h / 谢谢，在阳光下不太容易阅读！$h",
        "dating_Penny": "I... I don't know what to say. I'm so happy...$l / 我……我太开心了，都要语无伦次了……$l",
        "Sun": "Hello. Ummm...$u / 你好。唔唔……$u#$b#The weather's interesting today, don't you think? / 今天的天气还真是特别呢，不觉得吗？#$e#Sorry...$u / 抱歉……$u",
        "divorced": "...Please, leave me alone.$s / ……求求你，离我远点。$s",
        "married_Maru": "That was a beautiful wedding. I know Maru will make you very happy, she's a great person. / 你们的婚礼好浪漫。玛鲁人特别好，你跟她在一起肯定会很幸福。",
        "event_speaker_no": "Really?... Uh... Well, alright. I guess I'll see you later then.%fork$s / 真的吗？……呃……唔，那好吧。那我们下次见吧。%fork$s",
        "event_family1": "Me too.$h / 我也是。$h",
        "Sun4": "I've been trying to keep our place clean, but it always gets messy again.$s / 虽然我一直都有注意，想保持房间清洁，但却总是乱糟糟的。$s#$e#It's hard to run a household all by yourself.$u / 自己一个人工作还要做家务真的很累。$u",
        "Mon8": "I'm eager to move out. It's such a burden to be worrying about Mom all the time. / 我其实很想搬出去住。每晚担心妈妈会不会喝多，真的很累。#$e#I want her to be happy, but I can't stay here forever... you know?$s / 我也想一直陪着她，让她高兴，但不能总这样下去啊……你明白的吧？$s",
        "summer_Fri": "$d bus#I heard you were responsible for fixing the bus back up. Thank you. / 听说是你把巴士修好的。谢谢。|My mother used to drive the bus to Calico Desert... but the bus stopped working a few years ago. Mayor says there's not enough money in the town coffers, or else he'd have it fixed. / 我妈妈以前是卡利科沙漠线路的巴士司机，不过巴士几年前坏掉之后，就失业了。镇长说镇上的预算不够，不然早就把巴士修好了。$u",
        "fall_Thu6": "Mom doesn't take very good care of herself...$u / 妈妈总是不好好照顾自己……$u#$e#I worry about her.$u / 让我很是担心。$u",
        "Fri4": "Dishes, dishes, dishes. Ugh... If my mother wasn't always nursing a headache from her late nights at the saloon, maybe she could help around the house a little.$s / 每天都要刷碗扫除。呃……如果妈妈每晚不喝酒，早早就回来按时睡觉，或许也能帮我做点家务呢。$s",
        "event_pool2": "Really? I thought you'd have noticed by now...$8 / 真的？我还以为你早就意识到了呢……$8",
        "Tue": "I'm tutoring Vincent and Jas today... They're a handful, but it's nice to make a difference in someone's life. / 今天我该去辅导文森特和贾斯了……他们两个虽然淘气，但能教书育人让我感到很开心。",
        "AcceptBirthdayGift_Negative": "For my birthday? That's so kind of you! Let me unwrap it...$h / 给我的生日礼物吗？你对我真好！我拆开看看……$h#$b#...What!?$12 / ……怎么回事？！$12#$b#...Oh, I see. It's a cruel joke.$s / ……唉，好吧。原来是个刻薄的玩笑。$s#$b#Silly me, I should've known better...$s / 我真傻，我早该明白的……$s",
        "Mon_7": "That's how I feel. I'm just going to focus on making the future better. / 我也是这么想的。只要集中精力让未来变得更好就是。",
        "fall_Sun10": "@! I was just thinking about the future... / @！刚刚我还在考虑自己未来的事情呢……#$e#Where do you picture yourself in ten years?$l / 你觉得十年之后的自己会是怎样的？$l#$e#I have a few ideas for myself...$u / 我自己倒是有一些考虑……$u",
        "event_family2": "...sorry.$s / ……抱歉。$s",
        "event_old3": "That's nice of you to say... I totally agree with you. / 你能说这话真好……我完全同意。#$b#We should treat our elders with the same respect we hope to receive ourselves some day. / 我们现在尊敬老人，老了之后才能获得尊敬。",
        "FlowerDance_Accept_Spouse": "I accept!$h / 我接受！$h#$b#*whisper* Thanks for going through with the formalities, dear. / *低声说*你这事情办的很正规，谢谢了，亲爱的。",
        "event_old2": "You're right, we shouldn't ignore the reality of aging.$u / 你说得没错。我们不能无视人的生老病死。$u#$b#I guess the sooner we come to terms with our mortality, the more time we can spend really living in the here-and-now.$u / 只要我们能够意识到生命的转瞬即逝，就能够更加珍惜当下的一分一秒了吧。$u",
        "AcceptGift_Positive_ancient_item": "Wow... this looks really old. I'll have to ask Gunther about it. Thank you!$h / 哇……这是个古董吧，我得拿去给冈瑟看看。谢谢你！$h",
        "Mon_old": "#$p 7#But if I keep trying I think I can get her to change.|I guess it makes sense. There's not much I can do to change it, anyway. / #$p 7#不过如果我继续努力，应该是能劝她回头的吧。|的确如此。这事我也没什么办法呢。",
        "Resort_Towel": "The wind keeps making me lose my page, but it feels really great on the skin.$h / 风总是把我的书页吹乱，吹在皮肤上的感觉真舒服。$h",
        "event_mail3": "I see. / 原来是这样。",
        "winter_Fri2": "Are you friends with Linus? He lives in a tent up in the mountains. / 你和莱纳斯是朋友吗？就是那个在山上搭帐篷居住的人啦。#$e#Everyone ignores him, the poor guy. He's actually really nice... Just a little odd. / 他被大家无视，总觉得有些可怜呢。他其实是个好人，只是行为有些怪异……#$e#It must be so cold to live in a tent this time of year. / 现在这么冷，住在帐篷里一定很受罪吧。",
        "eventSeen_34_memory_fourweeks": "I'm teaching the kids about art history this week. / 我这星期在给孩子们讲艺术史。#$b#It can be a little dry for the kids, so I'm having them learn by drawing a picture in the predominant style of each century. / 孩子们可能会觉得有点枯燥，所以我就让他们用每个世纪的主流风格画一幅画。#$b#It's really been a hit!$h / 他们真的很喜欢！$h",
        "event_cook3": "Oh...I'm sorry.$s / 哦……很抱歉。$s",
        "dating_Penny_memory_twoweeks": "I never thought my life would be more exciting than a novel, but it sure feels that way right now!$h / 我一直觉得人生不可能像小说那样精彩，可是现在真的有那种感觉了！$h",
        "Mon4": "*sigh*... My mother definitely has a problem with going to the saloon too much.$s#$q 7/8 Mon_old#But it's best not to dwell on bad things, right?#$r 7 50 Mon_7#Right. It's best to be positive!#$r 8 10 Mon_8#I think it's good to be realistic. / *唉*……我妈每天晚上都去酒吧喝酒，怕是上瘾了。$s#$q 7/8 Mon_old#但果然还是不要总想着消极的一面吧？#$r 7 50 Mon_7#没错。还是保持乐观比较好哦！#$r 8 10 Mon_8#还是现实一点比较好吧。",
        "fall_Mon4": "It's kind of embarrassing to be the only family in town who lives in a trailer.$u / 全镇的人里只有我们家住在房车里，感觉有些丢人呢。$u#$e#I wish I could live in a nice house, someday.$s / 真希望有朝一日能住在真正的房子里面。$s",
        "AcceptGift_Positive_book_item": "Thank you! I'm almost finished with a book right now, but I'll read this one next!$h / 谢谢你！我现在读的书马上就看完了，接下来我就看这本！$h",
        "Wed4": "I've lived in Pelican Town my whole life. Can you believe that? / 我这一辈子都是在鹈鹕镇度过的。想想也真是有些难以置信。#$e#I guess there's a lot out there I'll never experience. / 这世上有许多事情，我怕是都见不到了。",
        "summer_Mon": "Hi... Um, nice weather, isn't it? / 你好……呃，今天天气还不错哦？",
        "event_speaker_kids2": "... Me too. I'm glad you feel that way.$7 / ……我也是。很高兴你也能这么想。$7",
        "fall_Fri": "Fall is a sad time of year for me...$s / 每到秋时总悲伤……$s",
        "event_speaker_yes": "Great!$h / 非常好！$h#$b#Let me just call the children over. / 我这就把孩子们叫过来。",
        "pamHouseUpgradeAnonymous": "There are some truly wonderful people in the world... / 世界上真有一些大好人……",
        "event_mail1": "Thank you...$l / 谢谢你……$l#$b#I just wish George wasn't so upset... I was only trying to help.$s / 真希望乔治不要那么难过了……我只是想帮忙而已。$s",
        "Sat": "This is such a small town. You can't avoid meeting everyone. / 镇子很小，所有人自然都十分熟络。#$e#I wonder what it's like to live in the city? / 不知城市里又是什么样的呢？",
        "eventSeen_35_memory_twoweeks": "I've been reading a book about the ocean. It accounts for most of the area of the world, and yet we hardly know anything about it! / 我最近在读一本讲海洋的书。这个世界大部分地方都是海洋，我们却几乎对它一无所知！",
        "winter_Mon": "On the 25th we'll be having the Feast of the Winter Star. It's one of my favorite events. / 25 号那天，会进行冬日星盛宴哦。这可是我最喜欢的节日了。#$e#It's supposed to be a time to show gratitude for all the good things in your life... but for most people it's just a time to relax and exchange gifts. / 这天本来是对生活中一切美好事物进行感恩的日子……不过现在大多数人只是趁这个节日好好放松一下，交换礼物罢了。",
        "Fri": "If you dig in the dirt you can find some interesting things. / 如果在土地上潜心挖掘，是会找出有意思的东西的。#$e#One time I found a really old piece of pottery. I brought it to Gunther and he said it was over a thousand years old. / 有一次我找到一块旧瓷器的碎片。拿去给冈瑟一看，他竟然说那东西有一千年以上的历史呢。",
        "Resort_Leaving": "I had a great time.$h / 我玩得很开心。$h",
        "fall_Fri6": "When I was a little girl, my father abandoned us because he said he felt 'trapped'. We haven't seen him since.$s / 我小的时候，父亲觉得我们是累赘，就抛下我们走了。自那时起就再没有见到过他。$s#$b#I'm sorry to make things uncomfortable for you... It's just that this time of year makes me think of it for some reason.$u / 抱歉，提起这种事一定让你很尴尬吧……只是每到秋天，就不由得想起这件事来。$u#$e#Anyway... How's the farming life going? / 话说……你的农场最近怎么样了？",
        "event_speaker_kids4": "Oh, really?$s / 真的吗？$s#$b# I think you'd make a good parent.$7 / 我觉得你很适合为人父母哦。$7",
        "married_Sam": "Congratulations, @. Sam's a lot of fun, I'm sure you'll never have a dull moment! / @，祝贺你。山姆人很有风趣，你跟他在一起不会无聊的！",
        "eventSeen_36_memory_oneweek": "Oh, pardon this bandage on my hand...$s / 啊，你说我手上的绷带啊……$s#$b#I went over to Maru's the other day and she showed me a new gadget of hers. The darn thing charred my palm!$s / 前几天我去了玛鲁家，她给我看了她的新发明，那破玩意儿把我手掌给烧了！$s"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/Pierre",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "fall_Thu": "It's starting to get cold outside... / 天气开始冷了……#$b#That means more people come into the shop to warm up... Hehe. / 也就是说更多人会来店里取暖……呵呵。",
        "GreenRain_2": "Glad to see you, @. What's a little toxic rain when you have seeds to buy?$h / @，你好啊，为了买种子，一点有毒的雨有什么好怕的，是不是？$h#$e#I'm just kidding. The rain seems to be completely harmless. / 我开玩笑的，这场雨好像完全无害。",
        "Fair_Judged_PlayerLost": "It feels great to be on top! Hah!$h / 屹立在顶点感觉可真棒啊！哈！$h#$e#Nice effort, though. / 努力总算是有成果了。",
        "winter_Wed": "$d joja#Finally... a day of relaxation. / 总算能休息一天了。|Now that Joja is gone, I feel a responsibility to keep the shop open seven days a week. People need groceries! / Joja 已经不在了，所以我觉得有责任一周七天都开着店，毕竟大伙都要来我这买东西！",
        "Resort": "I'm losing a lot of money being away from the shop...$s / 我没有开着商店，所以会亏很多钱……$s#$b#But, you know what? It's worth it. / 不过你明白吗？这是值得的。",
        "Thu2": "I really do appreciate your business, Mr. @. I've been having a harder and harder time turning a decent profit. / 真的很感激你的惠顾，@先生。最近想要盈利真的是越来越难了。^I really do appreciate your business, Ms. @. I've been having a harder and harder time turning a decent profit. / 真的很感激你的惠顾，@女士。最近想要盈利真的是越来越难了。",
        "Thu": "I'm happy to buy any produce off you. / 如果有农产品的话，卖给我也可以哦。#$b#I'll give you a fair price, of course! / 当然了，价格绝对包你满意！",
        "summer_Thu": "Everyone's enjoying the weather instead of shopping... *sigh* / 大家都在外面踏青，没人想来买东西……*唉*",
        "Sat8": "I'll tell you a secret. Sometimes, when the store is empty, I'll practice my opera singing behind the counter.$h / 告诉你个秘密好了。店里客人少或者快打烊时，我会在柜台后面练习美声。$h#$e#Don't tell anyone. / 不要告诉任何人。",
        "Introduction": "Hey, it's Mr. @, the new farmer! I'm Pierre, owner of the local general store. / 嘿，您就是新来的农夫@先生吧！我是皮埃尔，镇上杂货店的店主。^Hey, it's Ms. @, the new farmer! I'm Pierre, owner of the local general store. / 嘿，您就是新来的农夫@女士吧！我是皮埃尔，镇上杂货店的店主。#$b#If you're looking for seeds, my shop is the place to go. I'll also buy produce from you for a good price! / 如果想买种子的话，来我这里就对了。而且我还会高价收购你的作物哦！#$e#A little agriculture could really inject new life into the local economy! / 有了农业发展，相信本地的经济也会振兴起来的！",
        "Fair_Judging": "Hey, good luck. / 嘿，祝好运。",
        "summer_Sat": "Summer is a good time to eat a refreshing salad, don't you think? / 夏天还是吃清爽的沙拉最合适，你也这么觉得吧？",
        "Mon": "Welcome! If you're looking for seeds, you've come to the right place! / 欢迎！如果想买种子的话，来我这里就对了！",
        "summer_Wed2": "$d joja#Running the shop is one of the most important things in my life, but sometimes you just need a day off... / 开店是我生活的重心，但有时候还是得休息一天的……|Now that Joja is gone, I feel a responsibility to keep the shop open seven days a week. People need groceries! / Joja 已经不在了，所以我觉得有责任一周七天都开着店，毕竟大伙都要来我这买东西！",
        "Tue6": "You know, I used to be a pretty good boxer back in the day... my right hook was the stuff of legend!$h / 我年轻的时候，可是个有名的拳击手……我的右勾拳简直是天下无敌啦！$h",
        "joja_Begin": "This is a sad day for Pelican Town... The stronger Joja becomes, the closer I move toward bankruptcy. I might have to sell the shop soon...$s / 这是鹈鹕镇悲伤的一天……Joja超市越强，我离破产就越近。我很快就会被迫卖掉这家店……$s",
        "MovieInvitation": "Hey, that's a great idea... It'll be nice to get out from behind the counter. I'll meet you there! / 哎呀，这主意真不错……从柜台后面出来走走是挺好的。那我们到那边见！",
        "GreenRainFinished": "Well, I'm glad things are back to normal. Seems like it was all overblown... just like everything. / 嗯，幸好一切都重回正轨了。感觉事情是被过分夸张了。",
        "Sun": "#$1 pierreBlue#*sigh*... I've got those behind-the-counter blues... / *唉* ……整天在柜台后面，都无聊死了。$k$s#$e#I wish I could go for a walk, but I can't leave the store unattended. / 其实我也想出去走走，可店里不能没人照应啊。#$e#I've heard the flowers are in bloom and the air smells great...$s / 听说最近花儿都开了，到处都是芬芳四溢的香气。$s",
        "Event_naga1": "Thanks, I appreciate that. Just forget you ever saw this, okay?$h / 谢谢你，感激不尽。你就当做没看见，好吗？$h#$b#...And I'll just forget that you were snooping around in my bedroom! / 而我也会忘记你随便进出我房间的事！",
        "Wed": "$d Joja#It's my day off today. / 今天是店里的休息日。#$e#Hmmm... what to do...$s / 唔……该做什么好呢……$s|If you find any wild produce, I'll take it off your hands for a reasonable price. / 如果你能找到山货，可以在我这里卖掉哦。",
        "AcceptGift_(O)Book_PriceCatalogue": "Gripping! Fascinating! It's the perfect book for me!$h / 实在是激动人心！我太需要这本书了！$h",
        "Mon_inlaw_Abigail": "Hello, er... ${my son^daughter}$?$s / 你好，呃……我的${儿子^女儿}$？$s",
        "fall_Sat": "I'm happy to buy whatever you produce on the farm. / 我愿意购买你的农场产生产的各种农作物。#$e#Yes, I do resell it for a profit... but that's the benefit of being an established shop owner. / 当然，我会通过转手销售获得利润……但这是我作为一家有口皆碑的商店主人的福利啊。#$e#Don't get any ideas... / 你别多想……",
        "Resort_Chair": "Eh, let the kids play in the sun. I'll just sit in this chair. / 啊，让孩子们在太阳底下玩耍吧。我坐在这里就好。",
        "cc_Complete": "This is a dream-come-true! You can't begin to imagine how much stress JojaMart was causing me. / 这真是“梦想成真”！你都无法想象 Joja 超市对我造成了多大压力。#$e#For a small town like this, one store is enough! There's too much social pressure for me to overcharge, anyway. / 对于这样的小镇来说，一家商店就够了！不管怎样，社会压力如此之大，我都无法宰客了。",
        "married": "Well, now that you have dual incomes, I expect you'll be purchasing twice as many seeds, right?$h / 嗯，既然你现在有双份收入了，种子也该买双倍了，对吧？$h#$b#Haha... I'm only joking.... *ahem*... / 哈哈……我就开个玩笑……咳咳……",
        "winter_Fri": "I mainly deal in edibles, so if you've got any ores or wood you'd better try selling them somewhere else. / 我主要交易食品，你要是想出售矿石或木材的话就得去找其他人了。",
        "summer_Fri": "Oh, hi. Are you satisfied with the quality of my summer seeds? / 嗨。怎么样，我的夏季种子质量还不错吧？",
        "winter_Sun": "If I didn't have this shop to run I would be outside right now. / 要不是要看店，我早就出去玩了。#$e#It would be fun to throw a snowball. / 这天气打雪仗挺好的。",
        "GreenRain": "Gahh, no customers! Any more of this 'green' rain, and my ledger will be in the 'red'!$s / 唉，顾客都不来了！这“绿”雨要是再下下去，我这店里就全是“赤”字了！$s",
        "fall_Mon": "Fall seeds are here! Crops don't grow in winter so this is your last shot until spring. / 秋天的种子到货了！冬天是种不了农作物的，所以这是今年的最后一次耕种了。#$b#Better go all out, huh? / 趁现在全力以赴吧？",
        "Tue": "Sometimes I get new items in stock, so make sure to stop by every so often. / 有时我会进新货品，所以平时没事的话，还是常来看看吧。#$e#It's a lot of work to run a shop.$h / 开商店还真是苦力活呢。$h",
        "AcceptGift_(O)StardropTea": "Wow, I can't believe you'd give this to me. It must've cost you a fortune! Thanks! / 哇，你居然要送我这个，肯定很贵吧！谢谢你！",
        "eventSeen_3102768_memory_oneweek": "I'm determined to keep my shop running until the bitter end.$s / 我下定决心了，不到破产绝不关店。$s#$b#Morris and his cronies will have to drag me out from behind the counter, kicking and screaming!$h / 莫里斯那帮人即使费九牛二虎之力，也别想把我从柜台后面拖出去！$h",
        "Event_naga2": "You would really do that to me? You're terrible.$s / 你真的要那样对我？你真卑鄙。$s#$b#You shouldn't have been snooping around in my bedroom in the first place! Nosy neighbors are the worst.$3 / 你本就不该随便进出我的房间！八卦的邻居什么的最讨厌了。$3",
        "married_Abigail_memory_oneday": "Hello, er... ${my son^daughter}$?$s / 你好，呃……${我的女婿^女儿}$？$s",
        "winter_Sat": "Is it just me or is there a cold draft in here? / 刚刚一阵寒风刮过，是我的错觉吗？",
        "eventSeen_4": "Abigail's going through a rebellious phase... I get it. / 阿比盖尔还在叛逆期……我懂的。#$e#She'll wise up when she has to make her first mortgage payment!$h / 等她到了要还贷款的年纪就会醒悟了！$h",
        "summer_Wed": "$d joja#I'm so glad to have a day off from work. / 今天终于不上班了，真开心。|Now that Joja is gone, I feel a responsibility to keep the shop open seven days a week. People need groceries! / Joja 已经不在了，所以我觉得有责任一周七天都开着店，毕竟大伙都要来我这买东西！",
        "Fair_Judged_PlayerWon": "I can't believe I lost...$s / 真不敢相信，我竟然输了……$s",
        "Resort_Shore": "Mmm... that salty smell of the sea is making me want some sashimi. / 唔……大海的咸味让我想吃生鱼片了。",
        "Mon4": "Hi, @. Need any seeds or fruit tree saplings? / 嗨，@。今天是来买种子和树苗的吗？",
        "Thu4": "Hey, @. You're my number one customer! / 嘿，@。你是我最爱的顾客哦！",
        "summer_Mon": "I've got summer seeds available! You'd better stock up. / 现在开始卖夏季种子了！还是赶紧囤积比较好哦。",
        "Wed4": "#$1 pierre1#*sigh*... No matter how well the business does, it's never enough to satisfy my desire for success. What's wrong with me? Maybe I'm just bored with domestic life.$s / #$1 pierre1#*唉*……不管生意有多好，总感觉还是满足不了我的成功欲。我到底是怎么回事？大概还是对这过于平淡的生活产生了厌倦吧。$s#$e#When I was younger I always had something interesting to do... now I find myself just wasting time whenever I'm not at work.$s / 年轻的时候，总是有好多有意思的事可以做……现在呢，不营业的时候我也只是消磨消磨时间。$s",
        "fall_Fri": "#$1 pierreMEGA#My dream is to keep opening new stores until I become extremely wealthy. Hehehe. / 我的梦想是建立无数分店、成为富豪。哈哈哈。$k#$e#Hi there. Is your farm still doing well? / 嗨。农场那边还顺利吗？#$e#Maybe a few of my seeds will spruce things up.$h / 也许我的种子能够为你带来大丰收呢。$h",
        "Mon4_inlaw_Abigail": "Hi, @. How's Abigail doing? The shop hasn't been the same without her... / 嗨，@。阿比盖尔怎么样了？没有她商店都不一样了……",
        "summer_Sun": "Ugh... It's so hot in here. / 呃……这里真的好热。",
        "Thu8": "#$1 pierre2#Does Abigail look anything like me? Don't tell my wife, but sometimes I wonder if I'm really the father. / 阿比盖尔真的长得像我吗？我跟你说的话你可别和我老婆乱说……但有时候我真怀疑我是不是真的父亲。$k$s#$e#Don't tell my wife, but I hate to cook dinner. / 别告诉我老婆啊……我其实很讨厌做饭的。",
        "Wed6": "$d joja#Some day I'm going to open a new shop in the city and make a killing. / 总有一天，我会去大城市里开一家新店，然后举世闻名！#$e#Unfortunately, business is so slow I can hardly save any money...$s / 不过，小镇里的生意再怎么好，也还是不景气，也攒不了多少钱呢……$s|Business has been pretty good since JojaMart closed down. / 自从 Joja 超市关门，生意就一直挺好的。",
        "Sat": "If you find any wild produce, I'll take it off your hands for a reasonable price. / 如果你能找到山货，可以在我这里卖掉哦。",
        "fall_Sun": "If I didn't have this shop to run I would be outside right now... / 要不是要看店，我早就出去玩了。#$e#The leaves look great and the mushrooms are sprouting. / 秋叶很美，蘑菇也破土而出。",
        "winter_Mon": "You can't grow any crops during winter... so I have no seeds to offer you. / 冬天是无法进行播种的，所以我也没有种子可以卖给你。#$e#It's really going to cut into our profits. / 这一下雪，咱们俩的收益就都没了呢。",
        "winter_Thu": "#$1 pierreDin#I'm going to surprise Caroline tonight with dinner and a bottle of Stardew Red. Don't tell anyone! / 我今晚要用烛光晚餐和星露红酒，给卡洛琳一个惊喜。可别告诉其他人！$k#$e#Hi. In the mood for a little shopping? / 嗨。要买点东西吗？",
        "Fri": "#$1 pierreJoja#Business has been slow since Joja moved into town. It's hard to compete with their selection. / 自从 Joja 公司进驻小镇后，我这里生意就不好了。本地的小杂货店，怎么可能和 Joja 比货物种类呢。$k$s#$e#Hi there. Is your farm doing well? / 嗨。最近农场怎么样了？#$e#Maybe a few of my seeds will spruce things up. / 也许我的种子能够为你带来大丰收呢。",
        "Resort_Bar": "Drink after drink... Gus must be making a killing! / 一杯接一杯的……格斯一定赚了不少钱！",
        "eventSeen_3102768_memory_oneday": "How can I possibly compete with Joja?$s / 这让我怎么跟 Joja 竞争？$s#$e#Their pockets are so deep, they can just sell at a loss until little guys like me are out of business... then they'll jack up their prices!$s / 他们财大气粗，可以先亏本销售，搞倒我这种小本生意……然后再抬高价格割韭菜！$s"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/rainy",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "Alex": "Hmmph. This is not good weather for sports.$s / 唔。这种天气不适合运动。$s#$e#Oh well, I can always lift weights inside.$h / 啊，不过在室内还是可以练习举重的。$h",
        "Marnie": "Hi @. You look like you're soaked...you poor thing!$h / 嗨，@。你都成落汤鸡了……可怜的孩子！$h",
        "Lewis": "Hi there, @. Taking a break? / 你好啊，@。今天可以偷个闲吧？#$e#I hope the river doesn't overflow...$s / 希望河水不会泛滥吧……$s",
        "Wizard": "Stormy days are the only time I can commune with certain elementals. / 暴雨天是我跟某些元素沟通的唯一机会。#$e#I don't expect you to understand. / 你不会明白的。",
        "Leah": "Maybe I should cook something new and exciting today. Something spicy. / 也许我今天该煮点新鲜刺激的菜肴。辣菜好像挺不错。",
        "Krobus": "Ah, the sewers are flowing quickly today. It'll get nice and humid in here... Just how I like it. / 啊，今天下水道水量很大。这里会变得十分潮湿……就像我喜欢的那样。",
        "Shane": "Hmm... this weather makes me thirsty.$s / 嗯……这天气让我觉得很干渴。 $s",
        "Haley": "I spent all morning doing my hair... now the rain could mess it up.$s / 我花了一整个早上弄这发型……但是一场大雨就给我毁了。$s#$e#*sigh* ... Life is hard sometimes. / *唉* ……生活有时确实不容易啊。",
        "Linus": "A warm rain is a pleasant way to get clean.$h / 暖暖的雨很适合当作沐浴。$h",
        "Gus": "There's nothing like a glass of dry red wine on a day like this, huh? / 这种天气最适合享受一杯干涩的红酒了，对吧？#$e#I love my job. Hehehe. / 我爱死我的工作了。哈哈哈。",
        "Robin": "The rain doesn't stop me from getting a job done!$h / 大雨阻止不了我完成工作！$h#$e#Although soggy wood isn't a joy to work with.$s / 虽说潮湿的木材很难处理。$s",
        "George": "It's awful cold, isn't it? What a rotten day. / 天气也太冷了吧？日子真难熬啊。",
        "Leo": "The valley is peaceful when it rains. / 下雨时山谷里很平静……#$e#To me... nature is someone I know, with different moods. / 对我来说……大自然就像是一个熟人，有着不同的情绪。",
        "Emily": "It never rains in Calico Desert... That's where my friend Sandy lives. / 卡利科沙漠从不下雨……我朋友桑迪就住在那里。#$e#I wish I could've visited her today.$s / 真希望今天能去拜访她。$s",
        "Harvey": "Hi @! Er... Read anything interesting in the library lately? / 嗨，@！额……最近在图书馆有发现什么好书吗？#$e#Heh. Well, um... I'll see you around then? / 呵呵。那个，呃……下次再聊？",
        "Sam": "Rain muffles sound, so I can play my guitar louder without my mom getting mad. Hehe.$h / 大雨掩盖了声音，现在我弹吉他再大声都不会被妈妈骂了。呵呵。$h",
        "Elliott": "Sometimes when I lay in bed I can hear a distant foghorn cut through the rain. / 下雨的时候躺在床上，隐约能听到远处传来雾角声。#$b#But when I look out the window I see only a curtain of gray. / 但是望出窗外只能看见灰蒙蒙一片。",
        "Evelyn": "When I woke up I heard dripping from somewhere... I think the roof might be leaking.$s / 我一醒来就听到哪里传来滴水声……应该是天花板漏水了。$s#$e#In the old days, George would've scampered right up and fixed it... *sigh*$s / 以前都是乔治负责爬上去修好的……*唉*$s",
        "Dwarf": "Rain... It's almost mythical to us. Some of us dwarves live our entire lives without ever experiencing it. / 雨……对我们来说就像神话故事一样。我们矮人一族有的人一辈子都没见过下雨。",
        "Jodi": "Did you wipe your boots off before coming in? Sorry... I just cleaned the floor. / 你进来前擦干净了靴子吗？抱歉……我刚刚才把地板擦干净。#$e#But you're always welcome in here! Heh.$h / 不过这里永远欢迎你！呵呵。$h",
        "Demetrius": "Greetings. Stay inside if you want to keep warm. / 你好。想要暖和的话就进来吧。",
        "Penny": "The raindrops are really loud on the metal roof of our trailer. / 雨滴打在我们房车的金属车顶上的声音非常响。#$e#...It's soothing, though.$h / ……不过挺好听。$h",
        "Maru": "When it rains I have a good excuse to work on my gadgets all day.$h / 下雨的时候我就有借口专心做我的小玩意儿。$h#$e#It must be kind of boring for you, though. / 不过这对你来说应该很无趣。",
        "Pierre": "Most people stay indoors on days like this... It's not good for business.$s / 这种天气下很多人都待在家里……生意不好做啊。$s",
        "Abigail": "The valley looks more interesting in the rain... don't you think? / 雨天的星露谷别有一番滋味……你说呢？",
        "Sebastian": "If you're lucky, you might see a frog in this weather. / 运气好的话，这种天气可能会看见青蛙。",
        "Pam": "Howdy, kid. Stayin' dry? / 孩子，你好啊。没被淋湿吧？",
        "Clint": "Today would be a good day to explore the mines... Who knows, you might find some rare ores. / 今天是探索矿场的好日子……运气好的话说不定能够找到稀有矿石。",
        "Caroline": "My garden is happy today.$h / 我的花园今天会很高兴。$h#$e#...and our water bill will be lower this month. / ……而且我们这个月的水费也会降低。",
        "Sandy": "I heard it's raining back home. Is that why you came here?$h / 听说家乡在下雨。你是为避雨才跑来这里的吗？$h#$e#I kind of miss the rain, actually...$s / 话说我有点怀念雨景了……$s"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/Robin",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "fall_Thu": "You're always welcome to visit us, even if you aren't in the market for a building upgrade!$h / 即使不是来购置房屋升级，我们也很欢迎你来聊聊天的！$h#$e#It can get pretty lonely up here in the mountains. / 山上的生活有时候是挺孤独的。",
        "GreenRain_2": "There's all kinds of good wood out there today. Better get chopping, huh? / 今天外面长出了很多上好的木材，是不是该去砍一砍了？",
        "Resort": "Wow, look at these structures!$h / 哇，看看这些建筑！$h#$b#I can tell they were made by a master builder. I'm really impressed! / 我能看出来，它们是大师级建筑家的手笔。真是太了不起了！",
        "Thu": "You're always welcome to visit us, even if you aren't shopping, you know.$h / 即使不是来买东西，我们也很欢迎你来聊聊天的。$h#$e#It can get pretty lonely up here in the mountains. / 住在山上有时候是挺孤独的。",
        "reject_866": "Hmm... when I think of flowers, I think of Evelyn. Maybe show this to her? / 嗯……关于花的话，我会想到艾芙琳。也许你可以把这个拿给她看？",
        "divorced_Maru": "Maru was crying through the night... We're all devastated...$s / 玛鲁哭了一晚上了……我们都心疼得不行……$s",
        "Introduction": "Have you met everyone in town yet? That sounds exhausting. / 你有拜访镇子上的所有人吗？听上去很累的样子。",
        "cc_Bridge": "Hey! I heard some weird noises last night, and woke up this morning to find the quarry bridge completely repaired! / 嘿！昨晚我听到一些奇怪的声音，今天早上醒来发现石桥完全修好了！#$b#It's a miracle of woodworking! / 这真是木艺奇迹！",
        "structureBuilt_Shed": "So, what are your plans with the new shed? The possibilities are endless! / 好了，你想用这个小屋做什么呢？生活有无尽可能！",
        "Mon": "Have I told you that I built our house from the ground up? / 我有告诉过你我们的房子是我负责建造的吗？#$e#It's definitely been the highlight of my career so far. / 这是我入行以来最伟大的成就之一了。",
        "MovieInvitation": "Ooh... Two tickets for tonight's show, huh? Sounds good! I'll meet you there.$h / 噢噢……我们俩一人一张票，去看今晚的节目吗？好呀！我们到时候见。$h",
        "GreenRainFinished": "I hope Demetrius is happy with the 'samples' he collected. Seems like his little science project is more important to him than his own wife. Hmmph.$6 / 希望德米对采集到的“样本”还满意吧，感觉他的那什么科学研究比老婆还重要，哼。$6",
        "cc_Begin": "Hey! I heard that Lewis showed you around the Community Center... It'd be great if you could fix that place up. It used to be a really nice building! / 嘿！我听说刘易斯带你参观了社区中心……如果你能修好那个地方，那就太好了。它曾经是一座很美的建筑！",
        "Sun": "I hope Demetrius doesn't blow the house up with those science experiments of his. / 希望德米特里厄斯做的那些实验不会把房子给炸了。#$e#I'm not even sure what he's working on. I think it has something to do with plants. / 我不知道他在研究什么，但好像是跟植物有关的。",
        "Fri4_inlaw_Sebastian": "Sebastian told me he's trying to quit smoking! I'm really proud of him. / 塞巴斯蒂安告诉我他正努力戒烟！我真为他感到骄傲。",
        "event_wood1": "Great, then this blueprint should be a piece of cake for you!$h / 太好了，那么这份蓝图对你来说一定是易如反掌！$h",
        "Wed": "Hey there, @. / 嘿，你好！@。#$e#I was just daydreaming about some new carpentry projects. / 我正在构思一些新的木工项目呢。#$e#Are you doing OK at your place? How's the woodwork in your cottage holding up? / 你的工作还好吗？你的小屋还结实吧？",
        "houseUpgrade_3": "So, are you getting into the aged wine business? I've heard it's very lucrative... if you have the patience. / 怎么说，你打算开始陈酿吗？听说可以赚大钱……前提是你要有耐心。",
        "structureBuilt_Fish Pond": "I mentioned to Willy that you got a new fish pond. He seemed really happy about it. / 我跟威利说你造了新的鱼塘，他好像很高兴。#$e#Apparently, he raised crabs when he was a young man. Called it a 'time-honored tradition'.$h / 他年轻的时候好像养过螃蟹，他自称是“历史悠久的传统”。$h",
        "married_Maru": "We'll all miss having Maru around the house, but I'm sure we'll still see her often! / 玛鲁不在家里了，我们很想念，不过我相信还是可以经常见面的！",
        "structureBuilt_Coop_memory_oneweek": "How's that new coop treatin' ya? I'll be excited to meet your new animals! / 新建的栏舍怎么样？如果能看看你养的新动物就好了！",
        "houseUpgrade_1": "It was fun working on your house. That might be some of the finest construction I've ever done!$h / 修你的房子还是挺开心的，我可是使出了十成功力！$h#$e#I hope you're enjoying the new kitchen. / 希望你喜欢新的厨房。",
        "Resort_Chair": "Hey @. You know, I was just thinking about how far the town has come since you first moved here. / 你好，@。我刚刚在想，从你最初搬到这里起，整座镇子发生了多少改变。#$b#You should really be proud of all you've done!$h / 你真的应该为自己的成就感到自豪！$h",
        "pamHouseUpgrade": "Our little plan worked out well, don't you think? Pam and Penny seem really happy. / 我们的小计划很奏效，你不觉得吗？潘姆和潘妮似乎真的很开心。",
        "cc_Complete": "I knew it from the moment you stepped off that bus, @... you were destined to be a town hero!$h / 我从你走下那辆公共汽车那一刻起就知道了，@……你注定会成为这座城市的英雄！$h",
        "divorced_Sebastian": "Sebastian's back in the basement... what happened between you two?$s / 塞巴斯蒂安又回地下室去了……你们发生什么了？$s",
        "structureBuilt_Stable_memory_oneweek": "So, have you been riding your new horse around town? / 你骑马在镇上逛过了吗？#$b#I imagine you're pretty sore, but you'll get used to it soon.$h / 一开始可能会腰酸背痛，不过很快就会适应的。$h",
        "winter_Fri": "My parents were bewildered when I told them I wanted to be a carpenter. / 当初我告诉父母我想成为木匠时，他们都听傻了。#$e#They were pretty old-fashioned. / 我父母是很墨守成规的人。",
        "summer_Fri": "We're pretty insulated from the rest of the world here in Stardew Valley. / 我们星露谷这里可算是与世隔绝。#$e#It has its pros and cons. / 有好也有坏。",
        "Fri4": "#$1 RobinSeb#I found an ashtray in Sebastian's room, and it smelled really weird. Should I be worried about this? / #$1 RobinSeb#我在塞巴斯蒂安的房间里发现一个烟灰缸，散发着奇怪的味道。我该不该担心？#$e#Sometimes I worry about Sebastian... he doesn't have many friends and doesn't really seem to care about his future very much... / 有时候我很担心塞巴斯蒂安……他没有多少朋友，而且对自己的未来漠不关心……#$e#I would talk to him about it but he never opens up to me. / 我一直想跟他聊聊，但是他总是不愿意对我敞开心扉。",
        "GreenRain": "That man is insane! Why does he have to go out there? We have no idea if this rain is dangerous!$u%noturn / 那家伙疯了吧！他干啥非得出去？这场雨危不危险我们还不知道啊！$u%noturn",
        "fall_Mon": "#$1 RobinMaru#Maru likes gems. She uses them in her inventions. / #$1 RobinMaru#玛鲁喜欢宝石。她需要宝石发明东西。#$e#So how are you and Maru getting along? / 你跟玛鲁合得来吗？",
        "Tue": "Hey, if you need any materials or blueprints, my shop is the place you're looking for! / 嘿，如果你需要什么材料或者蓝图，请到我的店里来！#$e#Plus, your business supports the local economy.$h / 而且，你的光顾能够为本地的经济贡献一份力量。$h",
        "AcceptGift_(O)StardropTea": "Wait a sec... you're giving me this? What a special treat! Thank you. / 等等……你要送我这个吗？这个礼物太特别了！谢谢你。",
        "event_wood2": "Well, then I have the perfect blueprint to get you started! / 那我这份蓝图就很适合你了！",
        "summer_Tue": "If you need any buildings on your farm upgraded, just ask me! / 如果你想要升级农场的建筑，告诉我就好了！#$e#You'll need to provide enough lumber and stone for the project. And it costs money, too. / 你只需为该项目提供足够的木材和石块。当然也需要花钱。#$e#But I'm sure you'll be pleased with the results!$h / 但我保证成果会让你满意！$h",
        "structureBuilt_Slime Hutch": "*phew*... Building that slime hutch was a lot of work... I'll need a day at the spa to recuperate!$h / 呼……造史莱姆屋可真是个大工程……我得泡一天温泉恢复一下！$h",
        "Sun2": "#$1 RobinDem#My husband almost set the house on fire last night with his science experiment. One of his beakers exploded and sent a fireball into the rafters! Thank Yoba I used fire-resistant lacquer when I built the place.$u / #$1 RobinDem#我丈夫昨晚做科学实验差点把房子给烧掉了。他的其中一个烧瓶爆炸了，对着房椽射出了一颗火球！由巴在上，还好我当初建造这间房子的时候用了耐火漆。$u#$e#Sorry if it smells weird in here, @. It's my husband's bizarre science project... / 如果有难闻之极的气味，请见谅，@。我丈夫又在搞奇奇怪怪的科学项目……",
        "winter_Sat": "Our house is in such a beautiful area, don't you think? / 我们家附近的景色是不是很美？#$e#Everything looks still after a fresh snow. / 刚下完雪后一切都如此安宁。",
        "reject_865": "Veggie salt? Sounds good, but I don't need it. / 植物盐？听起来不错，但我不需要。",
        "Sun6": "Hi @! It's good to see you. / 嗨，@！很高兴见到你。#$e#You're a regular member of the community now, don't you think? / 你不觉得自己已经融入了这个社区吗？",
        "Fri_inlaw_Sebastian": "I miss my Sebby... he was always a little misunderstood, but I believed in him. / 我想念小巴……他以前总是被人误解，但是我相信他。",
        "Resort_Shore": "Hey, look! I can see another island from here. / 嘿，瞧啊！我可以从这里看见另一座岛。",
        "summer_Mon": "Wood is a wonderful substance... it's versatile, cheap, strong, and each piece has its own unique character! / 木材是一种很棒的东西，它的用途很多，便宜又结实，每一块都具有独特的性质。",
        "fall_Fri": "Have you met the wild man that lives behind our house?$s / 你遇见住在我们房子后的那位野人了吗？$s#$e#I guess I don't really mind, as long as he doesn't bother us. / 只要他不打扰我们，那我也不在意他的存在。",
        "structureBuilt_Barn_memory_oneweek": "Are you satisfied with the new barn? I'm sure you'll raise some very happy livestock in there! / 新建的畜棚还满意吗？牲畜待在里面肯定会很开心！",
        "pamHouseUpgradeAnonymous": "Our little plan worked out well, don't you think? Pam and Penny seem really happy. / 我们的小计划很奏效，你不觉得吗？潘姆和潘妮似乎真的很开心。",
        "Sat": "Our house is in such a beautiful area, don't you think? / 我们家四周的景色是不是很漂亮？#$e#I love the fresh air of the mountains. / 我喜欢山上的清新空气。",
        "winter_Fri_inlaw_Sebastian": "I think the farm life is really healthy for Sebby. / 我觉得农场生活对小巴来说很健康。",
        "winter_Mon": "Hey, it's a perfect time of year to gather wood. / 这是一年中最适合采集木材的时候了。#$e#Maybe you can collect enough to upgrade your house! / 也许你能够找到足够的木材升级你的屋子！",
        "AcceptGift_(O)SkillBook_2": "Ah, 'Woodcutter's Weekly'... I was hoping to get my hands on the newest issue! They've got all the latest techniques in here! / 啊，是《樵夫周刊》……我一直想要最新一期的！里面有很多最新的技巧！#$b#From one woodcutter to another... Thank you.$h / 砍树可是一门技术活……谢谢你。$h",
        "Fri": "You've met my son Sebastian, right? He lives downstairs. / 你遇见我的儿子塞巴斯蒂安了吗？他就住在楼下。#$e#He's a little shy, but I'm sure he'll warm up to you if you're nice to him. / 他为人害羞，但是你对他好，他一定会把你当朋友的。",
        "structureBuilt_Coop": "That's probably the sturdiest coop I've ever built. Hope you get a lot of use out of it! / 这个栏舍我修得可结实了，希望你能充分利用！",
        "Resort_Leaving": "That was fun!$h / 真是有趣！$h",
        "married_Sebastian": "Oh, don't worry... these are tears of joy. I know Sebastian will be very happy on %farm Farm!$h / 啊，不用担心……我这是太高兴了。我相信塞巴斯蒂安在%farm农场肯定会很幸福的！$h",
        "Resort_Bar": "This is so relaxing... / 真是太舒服了……",
        "houseUpgrade_2": "What are you going to do with all that new space in your house? / 新的房间你打算用来干什么呢？#$e#Or perhaps I should call it... your 'mansion'?$h / 你这也算是住上豪宅了吧！$h",
        "AcceptGift_(O)Book_Woodcutting": "What's this... 'Woody's Secret'? ... Um, what kind of book is this, @?$6 / 这是啥……《阿木的秘密》？……呃，@，这是什么书啊？$6#$b#Oh, it's about woodcutting! Hahaha... Oh yeah, I'm going to love this. Thanks!$4 / 嗐，是伐木的书啊！哈哈哈……哎，我肯定爱看的，谢谢你！$4"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/Sam",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "summer_Tue4": "Hi, @. Do you want to hang out or something? / 嗨，@。你想出去走走吗？#$e#I'm so energized during summer I hardly have to sleep! / 一到夏天我就特别兴奋，简直难以入睡！",
        "winter_Sat4": "I just remembered I need to change the strings on my guitar. / 我刚想起需要为吉他更换吉他弦。#$b#Okay, I'm going to write a note on my wrist so I remember to do it tonight. / 好，我得在我的手腕上记下今晚要做的事。#$e#I have to make little reminders for myself or else I'll totally forget to do things.$h / 我必须常常给自己做小提示，否则就会忘记得一干二净。$h",
        "Resort_Entering": "Wow, what a spot! / 哇，真是个好地方！",
        "Resort_Towel_2": "Maybe I should learn to play the ukulele. / 我是不是该学一下尤克里里……#$e#Abby on the congas and Sebastian on the steel drums... 'The Pelicans of Paradise'...$s / 阿比在打康茄鼓，塞巴斯蒂安在打钢鼓……“天堂的鹈鹕”……$s#$e#What's the matter, you look worried.$h / 怎么了，你看上去忧心忡忡的。$h",
        "Thu": "The clouds look great this time of year, don't they? / 每年这个时候，云彩都会很好看，不是吗？#$e#Like scoops of vanilla ice cream floating on blue raspberry sauce... Or maybe I'm just hungry. / 就像香草味雪糕漂浮在蓝莓酱上……或许只是我饿了。",
        "summer_Thu": "Dad was telling me about our national enemy, the Gotoro Empire... They sound like a ruthless bunch. / 父亲说我们国家的敌人，戈特洛国……他们都是无法无天的坏蛋。",
        "fall_9": "I ordered a new pair of shoes online. They're the same style so I know they'll fit right. / 我在网上订购了一双新鞋子。跟这一双一样的款式，应该会合脚。",
        "dating_Sam_memory_oneday": "I couldn't sleep last night. I was imagining all the things we're gonna do together.$10 / 我昨晚睡不着，一直在想我们将来会一起做的事情。$10",
        "fall_Tue": "My shoes always seem to wear out this time of year. Look, my toe's poking through!$h / 每年这个时候，我的鞋子就会坏掉。你看，我的脚趾头都露出来了！$h#$e#That's what happens when you skateboard too much. / 这就是滑板滑多了的代价。",
        "summer_10": "I don't have to work tomorrow! I've never been so happy.$h / 明天不用上班！好开心。$h",
        "Introduction": "Hey, I'm Sam. Good to meet you.$h / 嘿，我叫山姆。很高兴认识你。$h",
        "fall_Mon2": "I like taking walks in the forest this time of year. The temperature is so comfortable. / 每年的这个时候，我都喜欢在林中漫步。这种温度实在太舒服了。#$e#...$h / ……$h",
        "Mon": "Hey, farmer. / 嘿，农夫。",
        "FlowerDance_Decline": "Hmm... I dunno. Maybe next year.$s / 嗯……我不知道。不如明年吧。$s",
        "winter_24": "The Feast of the Winter Star is supposed to be a time to show gratitude for all the good things in life. / 冬日星盛宴的初衷是提醒大家要对世间万物抱有感恩之心。#$b#Me? I'm mostly interested in the food. Hehe.$h / 我？我只对美食有兴趣。呵呵。$h",
        "fall_Wed": "Hey... something smells good, like pizza. / 嘿……好香的味道，似乎是披萨。#$e#Do you smell that? Maybe Mom's cooking something. / 你闻到了吗？也许是妈妈在煮东西。",
        "Wed": "I'm trying to come up with a new song for my band, but I'm blanking...#$q 19/20 Wed_old#Hey.. What do you think my new song should be about?#$r 20 30 Wed_20#Farming, mining, and chopping wood.#$r 8820 30 Wed_20#A city in the sea.#$r 8821 30 Wed_20#Trains.#$r 19 -50 Wed_19#Choose anything. It'll still be a horrible song. / 我正在为我的乐队创作新曲，但是我完全没有灵感……#$q 19/20 Wed_old#嘿……你觉得我的新歌该是什么主题的？#$r 20 30 Wed_20#耕种、挖矿和砍柴。#$r 8820 30 Wed_20#海中之城。#$r 8821 30 Wed_20#火车。#$r 19 -50 Wed_19#随便吧。反正都是难听死的。",
        "fall_Fri10": "I think I've grown to like the country more than the city.$h / 我本身就比较喜欢乡下的生活。$h#$b#Although I could be biased... for a certain reason.$10 / 也许我是因为某种原因……而有这样的偏见吧。$10#$e#So, how are you doing today?$h / 话说，你今天工作顺利吗？$h",
        "fall_Sat": "Hmm. I think I was meaning to do something... But I forgot. / 嗯。我才想起我好像需要做某件事……但又不记得是什么事了。#$e#This happens to me all the time. / 唉，我总是那么善忘。",
        "fall_26": "Tonight, after everyone is asleep, that weird old man who lives in the woods will set up the haunted maze. He always makes sure no one is around to see him working. / 今晚夜深人静后，那位住在林子里的奇怪老头会打造那个闹鬼迷宫。他要确保没有人发现他的所作所为。",
        "AcceptBirthdayGift_Positive": "Hey, hey, hey! You remembered! Now that's what I'm talking about!$h / 哦哦哦哦！你还记得啊！这就对了嘛！$h",
        "fall_Sun8": "The first week of fall is already over. Man, that went by fast.$s / 秋天第一个星期就这样过去了。时间过得好快啊。$s#$e#Whatever. I'm just happy that you came to visit me! / 不管如何，很高兴你来拜访我！#$e#So do you have anything new to tell me? / 你有什么好消息告诉我吗？",
        "winter_Fri": "The worst thing about the snow is getting your feet soaked. You're lucky in those thick boots. / 冬天最糟糕的事情莫过于双脚在雪中湿透。你很幸运穿着一双厚厚的靴子。",
        "event_snack1": "${He's^She's}$ right... That's what happened.$s / ${他^她}$说得对……当时就是那样的情况。$s",
        "Thu6_2": "...I have mixed feelings about my father being back. He seems strange.$s / ……我对我父亲的归来有点忐忑不安。感觉他变得很奇怪。$s#$b#But I guess I haven't seen him in 3 years... so that could explain it. / 不过我也 3 年没见他了……也许是生疏了吧。",
        "Thu2_2": "Well, my Dad is back. Have you met him? / 我父亲回来了。你见到他了吗？#$b#I'm just glad he's okay. / 很高兴他平安归来。",
        "winter_Sun": "Try not to make a mess in the house or my Mom will flip. / 尽量别把家里弄乱，否则母亲就要发火了。",
        "GreenRain": "Whaa! Is it acid? Will it burn through the roof and sizzle us alive?$8 / 哎呀！下酸雨了吗？会不会把屋顶腐蚀穿了，然后活活烧死我们？$8#$b#I gotta keep my little brother safe!$7 / 我得保护好我弟弟！$7",
        "fall_Mon": "Oh, hi. Are you making friends with anyone in town? / 嗨。你在镇子上有交到好朋友吗？#$e#Bye. / 再见。",
        "breakUp": "Wait... what?!$8 / 等等……什么？$8#$b#I thought we were doing okay... I guess I was way off... alright, then.$9 / 我还以为我们相处得不错……可能是我完全搞错了吧……那……行吧。$9#$b#Yeah, sure... we can still be friends.$9 / 嗯，好的……我们还能当朋友。$9",
        "AcceptGift_(O)StardropTea": "Whoaa... Hold on... this is for me? I never expected this! Thank you!  / 哇……等等……这是给我的？太惊喜了！谢谢你！",
        "Tue4": "Hi, @. Do you want to hang out or something? / 嗨，@。你想出去走走吗？#$e#Sleeping feels nice but sometimes I wish I could skip it... it's just such a time-waster. / 睡懒觉是很爽，但有时候我真不想睡……因为太浪费时间了。",
        "summer_Tue": "Oh, hi! It's good to see you again. / 啊，你好！很高兴再次见面。#$e#Goodbye for now. / 下回再聊。",
        "summer_Mon2": "Hey, how's it going? / 嘿，怎么样了？#$e#I'm hungry. / 我饿了。#$e#See you later. / 下次见。",
        "dating_Sebastian": "I heard you and Sebastian are going out... he better still be coming to band practice every week! / 听说你跟塞巴斯蒂安在一起了……我看他每周还来不来乐队练习！",
        "dating_Sam": "Um... So, can I get a kiss now?$l / 唔……现在可以亲一下了吗？$l",
        "eventSeen_733330_memory_oneday": "If... I mean when... my Dad gets back, I wonder if he'll be the same as I remember him?$s / 如果我爸回来……我是说到等他回来的时候……还会跟我记得的他一样吗？$s",
        "FlowerDance_Accept": "Oh... with me? Hehe... Yeah, sure. Sounds fun!$10 / 啊……跟我吗？嘿嘿……好啊。感觉会很有趣！$10",
        "Thu6_1": "I think my Dad might be coming back in a year or so. / 我觉得我父亲大概会在一年内回来。#$e#I guess you might be able to meet him, then. If you're still living here. / 如果你那时还住在这里的话，你就能见到他了。#$e#You wouldn't abandon the farm after putting so much effort into it! / 你下了那么多功夫在你的农场上，应该不会抛弃它的吧！",
        "Resort_Shore": "Check out these gnarly waves... Guess what? I'm gonna save up for a surfboard. / 这海浪好大……你猜怎么着？我要攒钱买个冲浪板了。",
        "Mon2": "Hey, how's it going? / 嘿，你怎么样了？#$e#Last night I practiced guitar for 4 hours straight. My fingers hurt like crazy.$s / 昨晚我连续练习了 4 个小时的吉他，手指都痛死了。$s#$e#Bye, I've got something to do... / 再见，我还有事要忙……",
        "Sat4": "Oh! I just remembered I'm supposed to call my Grandma. Okay, I'm going to put this rubber band on my wrist so I don't forget. / 噢！我刚想起我得打电话给我的祖母。我先把这条橡胶圈绑在手腕上提醒自己。#$e#I have to make little reminders for myself or else I'll totally forget to do things.$h / 我必须常常给自己做小提示，否则就会忘记得一干二净。$h",
        "summer_Thu6_2": "Sometimes I can hear my Dad pacing down the hallway at night.$s / 有时候我会在晚上听到我爸在走廊里来回踱步。$s#$b#...But he won't tell us what's troubling him. / ……可他就是不肯告诉我们他在烦恼什么。",
        "summer_Sun": "When you see hot air balloons drifting over the sea, you'll know that summer's in full swing. / 当你看见热气球漂浮在大海上空，你就知道已经进入了盛夏。",
        "Wed6": "I've been friends with Sebastian for a while. He's a pretty cool guy. / 我跟塞巴斯蒂安认识很久了。他是个挺有趣的家伙。#$e#If you two weren't around I wouldn't really have any friends in town. / 除了你们俩人，我在这里都没有其他的朋友了。",
        "AcceptGift_(O)206": "Aw yeah... Pizza time!$h / 啊哈……该吃披萨了！$h",
        "fall_Sun": "It's hard to have fun on Sunday... I keep thinking about having to go to work tomorrow.$s / 一想到明天要回去上班……星期天就变得不开心了。$s",
        "winter_Thu": "My Dad is in the military, fighting against the Gotoro Empire. That's why he's not here. / 我父亲是军人，在跟戈特洛打仗。所以他人不在这里。#$e#He's coming back soon, though. / 不过他很快会回来。",
        "fall_Tue4": "Hi, @. Do you want to hang out or something? / 嗨，@。你想出去走走吗？#$e#Just stop by whenever you want. / 随时可以来找我。",
        "winter_Sun8": "It would be fun if we could go sledding, wouldn't it? / 要是能去玩雪撬就好了，你说呢？#$e#I don't think there are any good hills nearby.$s / 不过附近没有适合的山丘。$s#$e#Plus, I don't have a sled. / 而且我也没有雪撬。#$e#So, how have you been doing lately? / 话说，你最近过得怎么样？",
        "Wed_19": "Hey, man... what the heck is your problem? Sorry I asked.$a / 我说兄弟……你有病啊？算了当我没问。$a",
        "fall_Thu6_1": "I think my Dad might be coming back next year. / 父亲可能会在明年回来。#$e#I guess that's kind of soon. Weird. / 是不是有些早，感觉有古怪啊。",
        "Wed_20": "Hey, you know what? That sounds perfect. Thanks!$h / 是吗？你这个主意很不错哦。谢谢！$h",
        "fall_Thu": "Did you ever notice all the spider webs that appear during the fall? / 你有发现秋天时到处都是蜘蛛网吗？#$e#If you get up early you'll see them covered in dew... like little stars. / 要是起床早的话，你就能看见上面布满露珠……就像星星一样。",
        "GreenRain_2": "You notice how warm this rain is? It feels alive... / 你感觉到了吗？这场雨挺暖和的，似乎有种生机……",
        "event_room1": "Oh, I see. / 原来如此。",
        "married_Abigail": "Hey, what's the big idea? You took my drummer!$8 / 喂，你这是什么意思？你抢走了我的鼓手！$8#$b#Haha, just kidding... Congrats!$h / 哈哈，跟你开玩笑的……新婚快乐！$h",
        "event_snack3": "What!? ${He's^She's}$ lying!$a / 什么！？${他^她}$在说谎！$a",
        "winter_Wed": "$d Joja#I hate working at JojaMart, but how else am I going to make money in this town? / 我很讨厌在 Joja 超市工作，但不得不为五斗米折腰啊。|I'm glad I work at the museum now. It's way more interesting than that depressing JojaMart ever was. / 我很高兴在博物馆工作。至少比沉闷的 Joja 超市有趣多了。",
        "Resort": "I bet there's some cool stuff deeper on the island. / 岛屿的深处肯定还有些有趣的东西。#$e#Willy said we have to stay here, though... some kind of liability issues or something.$s / 但是，威利让我们必须待在这里……大概是出于安全责任的考虑吧。$s",
        "Thu2": "My Dad is a soldier, fighting against the Gotoro Empire. That's why he's not here... / 我父亲是位士兵，正在抵抗戈特洛国。所以他人不在这里……#$e#He'll come back someday. / 总有一天他会回来的。#$e#...I've heard some terrible things about the Gotoro Empire...$s / ……我听说过戈特洛国的很多可怕传言……$s",
        "winter_Thu6_1": "I think my Dad is coming back this spring. / 我父亲应该会在下个春天回来。#$e#It's been 3 years since I've seen him. This is going to be strange. / 已经 3 年没见到他了。见面时会很奇怪吧。",
        "Wed_old": "$p 19#But I already know what you think about it.$a / 但我已经知道你的想法了。$a|Thanks to your help I'm already done with the lyrics!$h / 谢谢你的帮忙，我已经想到歌词了！$h",
        "eventSeen_45_memory_oneweek": "Wouldn't it be cool if the town had a skate park, though? / 我在想，要是镇上建一个滑板场就好了。#$b#Now, how to convince Mayor Lewis...$s / 要怎么说服刘易斯镇长呢……$s",
        "firstVisit_Sewer": "Heheh... So you've been to the sewer, huh? I've snuck down there a few times myself. It's pretty creepy. / 嘿嘿……你去过下水道了吧？我自己也偷偷下去过几次，有点渗人。#$e#How could I tell? Hmm... let's just say... 'the nose knows'.$h / 我怎么看出来的？呃……这个嘛……有味道的呀。$h",
        "winter_Thu_2": "One thing that's nice about winter... all the mosquitos are gone. / 冬天要说有哪一点好……莫过于全部蚊子都消失了。",
        "secondChance_Guys": "Alright, I'm done with the cold shoulder act. Let's just forget about what happened.$7 / 好的，我受够了冷战。让我们完全忘记发生过什么。$7",
        "winter_Mon2": "Everyone's indoors during the winter, so I can play guitar as loud as I want.$h / 冬天时大家都待在屋里，所以我可以很大声地弹吉他。$h",
        "Event_band2": "Hey, you know what? That's exactly the kind of style I've been thinking about... for the band. / 嘿，你知道吗？这恰恰是我觉得乐队该走的风格。",
        "summer_Mon6": "Have you been to the desert yet? / 你到过沙漠吗？#$e#You can find some interesting things there. Dad took me a couple times when I was younger. / 那里有很多有趣的事物。小时候父亲曾经带我去过几次。",
        "summer_Wed2": "I saw a spider on my ceiling last night. They sure like the warmth. / 昨晚我看见天花板上有只蜘蛛。它们是喜热的生物。#$e#I hope he didn't crawl into my mouth while I was asleep...$s / 希望它没有趁我睡着时爬进我的嘴巴。$s",
        "winter_Tue": "Oh, hi! It's good to see you again. / 啊，你好！很高兴再次见面。#$e#Take it easy. / 不要那么紧张嘛！",
        "winter_7": "One time, Gus fell in the river during the Ice Festival. We had to build a huge fire in the saloon to dry him out. / 有一次在冰节时，格斯掉进了河里。我们在酒吧弄了一个巨大的篝火才烘干了他。#$e#We were all worried we'd never taste his famous spaghetti ever again. / 当时大家都很担心再也尝不到他的美味意大利面了。",
        "winter_Tue4": "Hi, @. Do you want to hang out or something? / 嗨，@。你想出去走走吗？#$e#Well, it's a good time of year to catch up on all the sleep I've missed.$h / 不过，每年这个时候都最适合补觉了。$h",
        "GreenRainFinished": "Seems like there's no damage to anything... That was a strange one. How are you holding up? / 好像全都完好无损……这场雨好奇怪。你没事吧？",
        "Fri10": "The older I get the more attached I feel to the valley. / 人越老啊，就越留恋这山谷。#$b#Although I could be biased... for a certain reason.$10 / 也许我是因为某种原因……而有这样的想法吧。$10#$e#So, how are you doing today?$h / 话说，你今天工作顺利吗？$h",
        "Event_band4": "Hey, you know what? That's exactly the kind of style I've been thinking about... for the band. / 嘿，你知道吗？这恰恰是我觉得乐队该走的风格。",
        "Sun": "Oh, it's a nice day... isn't it? / 哦，真是风和日丽的一天……不是吗？",
        "divorced": "I'm sorry, @. I don't think I can still be your friend.$s / 对不起，@。我想我没法再做你的朋友了。$s",
        "Wed10": "Hey buddy. You look like you're full of energy today! / 嘿兄弟。你今天好像朝气勃勃的样子！^@. Um... I just wanted to say... You look nice today.$10 / @。呃……我只是想说……你今天看起来很好看。$10",
        "fall_14": "Hi @. / 嗨，@。#$e#Hmm.. I wonder if I could grow a cactus in my room? / 嗯……不知道我能否在房间里种棵仙人掌？",
        "Mon8": "I'll tell you a secret... my name 'Sam' is short for 'Samson'.$10 / 告诉你一个秘密……我的名字“山姆”其实是“山姆森”的缩写。$10#$e#Most people don't know that so keep it on mute. / 很多人都不知道，你也别告诉别人。",
        "Sun8": "Sometimes I wonder if my mother is actually happy with her life...$s / 有时候我不禁在想，母亲这辈子真的幸福吗……$s#$e#I asked her once and got the feeling she was hiding some inner pain. / 我曾经问过她一次，感觉她在隐瞒着一些内心的痛苦。",
        "event_room2": "Yeah... That's what happened! / 对……就是那样的！",
        "winter_Thu6": "Dad's been back for a while now. I guess I'm finally getting used to it. / 父亲回来一阵子了。我终于开始习惯了下来。",
        "spring_21": "Sometimes those spring petals that float around make my nose drip.$s / 有时候这些随风飘扬的春天花瓣会弄得我流鼻涕。$s#$e#I like summer best, myself. / 我个人最喜欢夏天。",
        "summer_Fri": "You know... I used to live in the city and I have to admit, this place is much nicer in the summer.$h / 你知道吗……我曾经是住在城里的。但不得不说，夏天待在这里更加舒服。$h#$e#The city is so hot with all that concrete. / 城里到处都是钢筋水泥，热死了。",
        "fall_Thu6": "I guess I should start thinking about moving out soon...$s / 我得考虑尽快搬出去了……$s#$e#...But I would miss Mom's fish casserole, so I dunno...$s / ……但是我很想一直吃母亲的砂锅鱼，好难办……$s#$e#I hate making decisions. / 我讨厌做决定。",
        "Thu_3": "*sigh*... what am I still doing here? / *唉*……我还在这里做什么？",
        "Fri4": "Dad used to work as a garbage man in the city. / 父亲曾在城里当过清道夫。#$e#You don't even want to know some of the things he found in people's trash. / 你无法想象他在别人的垃圾中发现过什么东西。",
        "Tue": "Oh, hi! It's good to see you again. / 啊，你好！很高兴再次见面。#$e#Take it easy. / 不要那么紧张嘛！",
        "AcceptBirthdayGift_Negative": "Hey, hey, hey! You rememb--$h / 哦哦哦哦！你还记——$h#$b#...*sniff*...*sniff*... what's that gnarly smell...?$8 / ……（闻了两下）……这是什么怪味……？$8#$b#...Oh.$5 / ……啊。$5",
        "event_snack2": "Yeah... That's what happened! / 对……就是那样的！",
        "fall_Sat4": "I'm lucky to have the biggest room in the house to myself. / 我很幸运，霸占了房子里最大间的房间。#$e#I guess there's advantages to being the oldest child. / 也许这就是身为长子的优势吧。",
        "spring_23": "Why couldn't the flower dance be today so I could get work off?$s / 为什么花舞节不是今天举行？那样我就能请假了。$s",
        "FlowerDance_Accept_Spouse": "Aw, I gotta put on that dorky suit again? I thought now that we're married... Well, alright.$s / 哦，我又得穿上那件傻乎乎的西装吗？我想既然我们已经结婚了……唔，那好吧。$s",
        "10": "Did you watch the game last night? / 你看了昨晚的比赛吗？#$b#Or wait, do you even have a TV set...? / 等等，你有电视机吗……？",
        "14": "Ugh, I stepped in something gross earlier... and I just bought these shoes.$s / 呃，我刚才踩到一坨不知什么东西……这双鞋可是我刚买的啊。$s",
        "summer_Wed": "Hi. Taking the day off? / 嗨。今天休息？#$e#Sounds interesting. / 听起来是不错的主意。",
        "fall_16": "I ordered some shoes online more than a week ago! Man, they're really taking a long time. / 我一个多星期前在网上订购了一些鞋子！天呀，这服务真是慢吞吞的。#$e#I guess we must really live in the middle of nowhere.$s / 看来我们居住的地方一定是偏僻极了。$s",
        "Resort_Towel": "%Sam is playing a jazzy tune on his guitar. / %山姆用吉他弹奏着爵士乐。",
        "fall_23": "Ah, my feet feel great in these new shoes. They're a little crisp, but they'll break in. Especially after I run through the haunted maze this weekend.$h / 啊，穿上这些新鞋子感觉好多了。虽然有点硬，但慢慢就会合脚了。尤其是在这个周末去闹鬼迷宫跑一圈后。$h",
        "summer_Mon": "There's a little less pollen in the summer... my nose is really happy. / 夏天时花粉要少许多……我的鼻子很舒服。",
        "Thu_2": "Well, my Dad is back. Have you met him? / 我父亲回来了。你见到他了吗？#$b#I'm just glad he's okay. / 很高兴他平安归来。",
        "fall_Fri": "I used to live in Zuzu City, you know. The biggest difference is the noise. It's never quiet in the city. / 我曾经住在祖祖城。那里跟这里的最大差别是噪音。城里可没这么安静。#$e#There's way more people around you, always. And it's always bright with city lights, even at night. / 那里总是人山人海。哪怕是夜晚都会灯火通明。#$e#I guess which setting you like depends on your personality. / 至于哪一种生活比较好，大概因人而异的吧。",
        "Event_band1": "Hey, you know what? That's exactly the kind of style I've been thinking about... for the band. / 嘿，你知道吗？这恰恰是我觉得乐队该走的风格。",
        "spring_12": "My little brother gets so excited for festivals. He's been talking about tomorrow's egg hunt all day. / 我的弟弟很期待过节。他一整天都在讨论明天的彩蛋大寻宝活动。",
        "Sat": "Hmm. I just remembered that I was meaning to do something... But I forgot. / 嗯。我才想起我好像需要做某件事……但又不记得是什么事了。#$e#This happens to me all the time. / 唉，我总是那么善忘。",
        "eventSeen_45": "I better lay low for a while. I wouldn't want to get on Mayor Lewis' bad side! / 我还是避避风头吧，我可不想再惹到刘易斯镇长了！",
        "eventSeen_4081148_memory_oneday": "Even with all the practice we did, I made a bunch of mistakes on stage... I hope no one noticed.$s / 我们练习了很久，在台上我还是失误了好几次……但愿没人注意到。$s#$e#It's kind of nerve-wracking to be in front of everyone!$h / 在这么多人面前表演还是很紧张的！$h",
        "winter_Mon": "Hi... Cold, isn't it? / 你好……很冷，不是吗？",
        "Event_band3": "Hey, you know what? That's exactly the kind of style I've been thinking about... for the band. / 嘿，你知道吗？这恰恰是我觉得乐队该走的风格。",
        "Fri": "Did I ever tell you we used to live in the city? / 我有告诉过你我们一家人曾经是住在城里的吗？#$e#There's a lot more stuff going on, but it's also kinda noisy and hectic... It's hard to say which is better. / 那里有趣多了，但是却很吵很忙碌……很难说哪种生活比较好。",
        "Resort_Leaving": "I'm feeling pretty good from all the sunlight.$h / 晒了这么多太阳，我感觉挺不错的。$h",
        "married_Sebastian": "Wow, I can't believe you and Sebastian got hitched. Times really are changing...$u / 哇，真不敢相信你跟塞巴斯蒂安结婚了，确实难以预料啊……$u#$e#Eh, it's alright, I'm sure he'll still have time to hang out. / 没事没事，我相信他还是有时间出来玩的。",
        "Resort_Bar": "I'm just getting juiced up, then it's back to the beach. / 我来喝一杯提提神，等会就回海滩。",
        "dumped_Guys": "...$a / ……$a"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/Sandy",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "GreenRain": "I heard there's a rare weather event in the valley. / 听说星露谷出现了罕见的天气。#$e#I wish it rained here sometimes...$s / 假如这里也能下雨就好了……$s",
        "Thu2": "That shady-looking guy in the back? I'm really not supposed to talk about it. / 房间后面的那个可疑的家伙？我不想多管闲事。#$e#Anyway... what's the weather like in the valley? / 话说……山谷里的气候怎么样？",
        "Thu": "That shady-looking guy in the back? I'm not supposed to talk about it. / 房间后面的那个可疑的家伙？我不想多管闲事。#$e#Anyway... what's the weather like in the valley? / 话说……山谷里的气候怎么样？",
        "Tue": "You can find coconuts and cactus fruits outside. Feel free to take as many as you can find. / 你可以在外面找到椰子和仙人掌果实。想要多少随便拿。#$e#They're oooh-yummy, too. Heeee!~$h / 都是非常美味的。嘻嘻！~$h",
        "AcceptGift_(O)StardropTea": "Wow, that's so rare... I can't believe you're giving this to me! Thanks, honey! / 哇，这个太少见了……你居然要送给我吗？亲爱的，太感谢了！",
        "married_Emily": "How'd the big day go? Emily came up a while ago and told me all about your plans. / 你们的婚礼怎么样？艾米丽之前跑过来跟我说了你们的事情。#$b#I'll have to come visit you two on the farm sometime! / 之后一定要去农场上看看你们俩！",
        "AcceptGift_(O)418": "Ahh... even in winter, Stardew Valley has beautiful flowers. / 啊……星露谷即使在冬天也能种出美丽的花朵。",
        "Mon": "Hello hello, sweetie! / 哈喽，甜心！#$b#I'm so glad that the bus is back in service. It was starting to get lonely out here. / 很高兴巴士恢复服务。我都开始感觉到孤独了。#$e#...I almost went out of business.$s / ……我差点都要关门大吉了。$s#$e#Hey, but now you're here to buy a whole bunch of seeds... right, sweetie?$h / 但现在有你来买种子了……对吧，甜心？$h",
        "Wed8": "Isn't it expensive, coming to the desert so often like you do? / 像你这样经常跑来沙漠不是花费很大吗？#$e#You must really like to see me, huh? Hmmm... $h||*sigh*... I do miss the beautiful flowers of Stardew Valley...$s / 你一定是很喜欢来见我，对吧？嗯…… $h||唉……我很怀念星露谷的漂亮花朵……$s",
        "AcceptGift_(O)402": "*sniff*... Mmm... sweet peas have the most wonderful smell. / （闻了一下）……嗯……香豌豆的味道最好闻了。",
        "Thu4": "Hey... I think I can trust you. You can keep a secret, right? / 嘿……我觉得你是信得过的人。你能够保守秘密的，对吧？#$b#*whisper* That guy in the back... it's some kind of exclusive club. I've never been inside myself, but they pay me a generous monthly rent so I don't ask any questions. / *低声说*后面的那个啊……是某间私人会所。我从没进过去，但是他们每个月给我很丰厚的租金，所以我不会去多管闲事。#$e#SOOOOoo! How's that Stardew Valley weather right now? / 啊！星露谷的天气怎么样了？",
        "Sun": "It's always sunny here, even in winter! / 这里四季如夏，哪怕是冬天都一样。#$e#Actually, it's a little hot for my tastes... my delicate skin burns quickly in the sun.$s / 其实是有点热得过分……我的皮肤很容易就被晒伤。$s",
        "Wed": "Why hello there! If you see my friend Emily in town, could you tell her I said 'Hi'? / 啊你好！如果你在镇上遇见我的朋友艾米丽，记得帮我打个招呼？#$e#Thanks!$h / 谢谢！$h",
        "Wed10": "Hey, it's @! I'm glad to see you, kid. I was starting to think you'd never come back! / 嘿，是@！很高兴见到你，孩子。我刚在想你会不会不回来了！#$e#If I didn't have this shop to run I'd come back to the valley with you for a day or two... just you and me on the old farm.$s / 要不是要经营这家店，我就会跟你一块回山谷一两天了……到旧农场里，就你我两人。$s#$e#You'll just have to visit me more often so I don't get depressed.$h / 你得多来看我啊，否则我就会很伤心。$h",
        "Sat": "Hi! Welcome to Sandy's Oasis, the number one destination in Calico Desert! / 嗨！欢迎来到桑迪的绿洲，卡利科沙漠的第一旅游胜地！#$e#*whisper* Did I sound professional?$h / *低声说*我听起来够专业吗？$h#$e#Make sure to check out our seasonal seed selection. / 请浏览我们的四季种子精品。#$e#You look really thirsty. Here, have a taste of this ice cold milk. [184] / 你看起来很口渴。来，尝尝这杯冰冻鲜奶。[184]#$e#Tasty, huh?$h / 好喝吧？$h",
        "AcceptGift_(O)18": "Oh, wow! Nothing says 'spring' like a Stardew Valley daffodil!$h / 哇！看到黄水仙就让我想到了星露谷的春天！$h",
        "Tue10": "Hi!~ Stay as long as you like. / 嗨！~待久一点啊。#$e#The air conditioning sure feels nice, doesn't it? / 这个空调感觉很不错吧？",
        "Fri": "You wouldn't have much luck farming out here, honey. / 在这里耕种不会有好结果，甜心。#$e#Well, unless you were a cactus farmer.$h / 除非你是想种仙人掌。$h",
        "Sun8": "Hi there, honey. Yep, it's just me, alone in this big old shop. Hmmm... / 嗨，甜心。没错，就是我，独自一人在这家老店里。嗯……#$e#Well, except for that creepy guy in the back. But he never moves a muscle, so I often forget about him. / 除了后面那位奇怪的家伙。但是他从来没有出过来，所以我都经常忘了他。",
        "Fri4": "My name's not really Sandy, you know. It's just good for business. / 我其实不叫桑迪。都是为了生意才这么叫的。#$e#But everyone calls me Sandy anyway, so I've just gotten used to it. / 不过现在大家都叫我桑迪，我也习惯了。",
        "accept_866": "A Stardew Valley rose? That's so lovely! Thank you!$h / 星露谷玫瑰？真是太漂亮了！谢谢你！$h#$b#Whenever I miss the valley, I'll smell this rose. Hehe.$h / 我要是怀念星露谷就闻一闻这朵玫瑰。嘿嘿。$h#$b#Here, take this. It's been on the shelf for 10 years and no one has bought it. You can have it! / 来，拿着这个。它已经在架子上待了十年，根本没有人买它。你拿走吧！"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/Sebastian",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "summer_Tue4": "I'm looking forward to the cold, damp season. Channeling my inner toad, I guess.$h / 我很期待寒冷潮湿的季节——也许我上辈子是一只青蛙。$h",
        "Fri8": "What's new?$h / 有什么新闻吗？$h#$e#I'll be at the saloon tonight destroying Sam at pool again.$h / 在今晚酒吧的台球比试上，我要大败山姆。$h",
        "Sun10": "I was just thinking about you...$l / 我刚还在想你呢……$l",
        "Event_game1": "Okay, that'll work. / 嗯，这样就行了。",
        "Resort_Entering": "I liked the boat ride. At one point you couldn't see any land at all.. / 我喜欢乘船。在旅程中，只能看到茫茫大海……",
        "winter_Mon8": "Do you ever think back on your old self with shame and embarrassment? / 你回忆往事的时候会不会感到悔恨、羞愧？#$e#I guess it's just part of growing up. / 也许这就是成长的一部分。",
        "Thu": "#$1 Sebastian1#I snuck into the caves last night and got a nasty cut from a rock crab. Don't tell anyone, okay? / #$1 Sebastian1#我昨晚跑进山洞里被一只石蟹割伤了。别告诉任何人，知道吗？#$e#Hi. / 嗨。#$e#...want something? / ……有什么事吗？",
        "summer_Thu": "I definitely don't want to go swimming, if that's what you're going to ask.$s / 要是你想找我去游泳，我可要先说好了，没兴趣。$s#$e#Oh, you just stopped to say hi? Sorry. / 啊，你是来和我打个招呼的？抱歉。",
        "Thu6": "Could you picture someone like me living on a farm? It seems ridiculous.$h / 你能想象我这样的人住在农场里吗？简直荒唐。$h",
        "fall_Tue": "Pumpkin spice this... pumpkin spice that... man, I do get sick of these seasonal fads. / 这也是南瓜味……那也是南瓜味……我的天，这种季节性的狂热真是太恶心了。",
        "summer_10": "Hehe... It might be funny to put something disgusting in the potluck soup tomorrow. Just don't poison anyone. / 哈哈……要是在明天的百乐汤里放点恶心的东西一定会很有趣吧。只要不让大家中毒就行。#$e#Why ruin the potluck? Hmm... I guess some people feel liberated when the rigid structures of society break down a little. Maybe I'm weird. / 你说为什么要毁掉百乐汤？嗯……我想，有些人在那些僵硬的社会结构与条条框框崩溃一点点的时候，会有获得自由的感觉吧。也许我只是太古怪而已。",
        "Introduction": "Oh. You just moved in, right? Cool. / 噢。你是刚搬进来的，对吧？好啊。#$e#Out of all the places you could live, you chose Pelican Town? / 那么多地方你不选，偏偏选中了鹈鹕镇？",
        "AcceptGift_(O)575": "Is that obsidian? This is exactly what I've been looking for... I'm gonna see if I can shape it into a dagger.$h / 这是黑曜石吧？我正好想要一块……我想试试把它削成一把匕首。$h",
        "summer_Sat": "I hope we're not having mushroom casserole tonight...$s||Oh no, is it cave carrot tacos night? ...*groan*$s / 但愿今晚不要又吃蘑菇炖锅……$s||别吧，今晚吃山洞胡萝卜卷饼？……呃……$s",
        "fall_Fri_old": "$p 62#You probably wouldn't like it.$s / 那估计你是不会对它感兴趣的。$s|I think you'd like it. / 那我想你会喜欢它的。",
        "Mon": "Um... need something? / 呃……有什么事吗？",
        "Event_cave2": "Really? It was making a lot of noise! / 真的？它很吵诶！",
        "Tue6": "Sam's really outgoing, so when we hang out he does most of the talking. / 山姆很开朗，我们出去玩的时候，基本上都是他在说话。#$b#That's fine with me!||Imagine if Sam was as reserved as I am... we'd hang out and never say a word.$h||Some people are talkers, others are listeners. I'm more of a listener. / 我觉得挺好的！||假如山姆跟我一样内向的话……我们出去玩大概会从头沉默到尾。$h||有些人善于表达，有些人善于倾听。我更喜欢倾听。",
        "summer_Wed6": "If you're depressed, everything seems stupid. But if you're feeling positive, then even the most mundane things will make you happy. / 情绪低落的时候，看什么都觉得很蠢；情绪高涨的时候，多么平淡的东西都会让你感到开心。#$e#How do you stay positive long term? I have no idea. / 怎么才能一直保持乐观呢？我不懂。#$e#...Maybe I'll figure it out some day. / ……也许有一天我会明白。",
        "dating_Sebastian_memory_oneyear": "Hey... It's been a year since we started dating, remember?$h / 哎……还记得吗？我们一年前在一起的。$h#$e#It's been the best year of my life...$l / 这是我人生最美好的一年了……$l",
        "Wed2": "Sam is probably my only friend in this town. / 山姆也许是我在镇上的唯一朋友。#$e#Well, Abby is nice too, but...$h / 阿比盖尔也不错，但是……$h#$e#Umm.. never mind. / 呃……算了。",
        "Resort_Wander_2": "I bet this place looks pretty cool in the rain. / 这个地方在下雨的时候看上去一定很不错。",
        "FlowerDance_Decline": "No... There's someone else I want to dance with. / 不……我想跟别的人跳舞。",
        "winter_24": "It's the eve of the winter star today. Better make sure you've got an empty stomach for the feast tomorrow. / 今晚是冬日星前夜。最好饿着肚子，为明天的大餐做准备哦！",
        "AcceptGift_(O)305": "$c 0.8#Whoa... This egg speaks to me... I'll put it on my desk. Thanks!$h#Hmm... I wonder, if I put this under my pillow, will it hatch? Hehe... only one way to find out.$h / $c 0.8#哇……这个蛋好像能跟我说话……我就放在桌子上吧，谢谢你！$h#唔……如果我把它放在枕头下面，能不能孵出小鸡？嘿嘿……试试就知道了。$h",
        "fall_Wed": "*yawn*... what time is it? I think I slept too much last night. / *哈欠*……几点了？我昨晚似乎睡得太久了。",
        "winter_Mon4": "Nothing surprises me anymore... nothing makes me laugh. / 不管看到什么我都能做到不惊不喜……#$e#Yeah, I know... I'm being a little dramatic. / 是的，我知道……我是说得有些夸张。",
        "Fri2": "*sigh*... If gas wasn't so expensive I'd ride my motorcycle to the city today. / *唉*……要是燃油没那么贵，我今天就会骑着摩托车去城里了。#$e#$q 15/16 Fri_old#So what do you do when you aren't working?#$r 15 0 Fri_bad#More Farming#$r 16 30 Fri_good#Comic books#$r 15 -30 Fri_bad#Shopping#$r 15 -30 Fri_bad#Sports / $q 15/16 Fri_old#那么你是如何打发空闲时间的？#$r 15 0 Fri_bad#继续耕种#$r 16 30 Fri_good#漫画书#$r 15 -30 Fri_bad#采购#$r 15 -30 Fri_bad#运动",
        "event_city2": "Yea... That's exactly how I feel, too.$l / 啊……我也是这种感觉。$l",
        "Wed": "What am I going to do today? / 今天我有什么事可以做的？#$e#Probably nothing. / 也许没有。",
        "Mountain_47_23": "I come here for the peace and quiet. / 我是被和平和安静吸引而来的。",
        "fall_Fri_good": "Hey, me too. There's nothing like a good fiction to push the boundaries of the imagination.$h / 我也是哦。阅读科幻作品最容易激发人的想象力了。$h",
        "summer_Thu10": "If you ever wanted to go swimming... I guess I'd do it.$l / 如果你什么时候想去游泳的话……我就和你一起去吧。$l",
        "fall_Sat": "I was *this* close to moping in bed the entire day. Kinda wish I had, now. / 就差*这么*一点，就能在床上赖一整天了。要是成功了多好。",
        "fall_26": "The Spirit's Eve festival is tomorrow. I really hope they have those skeletons on display again this year.$h / 明天就是万灵节了。但愿今年会把那些骷髅拿出来展示呢。$h#$e#I almost feel like they're my friends at this point. / 我总感觉自己都和那些骷髅交上朋友了。",
        "AcceptBirthdayGift_Positive": "Oh, really? I wasn't expecting this. It looks great, though. Thank you.$h / 哇，真的吗？没想到你会给我这个，不过看起来很不错，谢谢你。$h",
        "winter_Fri": "It's fun to live so close to the train tracks. It's a reminder that there's a big world out there. / 住在火车道附近可是很有趣的。这总能提醒我外面的世界十分广阔。",
        "summer_Fri6": "Hey, I'm glad you stopped by.$h / 嘿，很高兴见到你啊。$h#$e#How have you been coping with this heat? / 这么热的天，你是怎么活下来的啊？",
        "AcceptGift_(TR)FrogEgg": "Hey, that's a frog egg! I'll see if I can get it to hatch. Thanks!$h / 哎，这是青蛙蛋吧！我要试试能不能孵出来，谢谢你！$h",
        "event_garage2": "Okay... Never mind then.$9 / 好吧……那算了。$9",
        "fall_20": "Are you looking forward to the Spirit's Eve festival? It's probably my favorite.$h / 你也在盼着万灵节吗？这可是我最爱的节日了。$h",
        "Fri_old": "$p 16#Hey, if you're bored feel free to hang out in my room...$h / 嘿，你无聊的话可以来我房间玩……$h|You probably prefer the small-town life, huh? / 你应该比较喜欢小镇生活，对吧？",
        "winter_Sun": "I built a snowgoon but Demetrius made me get rid of it. / 我堆了个怪物雪人，德米特里厄斯逼着我拆掉了。#$e#What's his problem?$u / 他这是有什么毛病啊？$u",
        "GreenRain": "My mom's freaking out, but I'm actually kind of enjoying this. I bet the frogs are going wild out there!$h / 我妈吓坏了，我倒是挺喜欢现在这样的。外面的青蛙肯定都兴奋得不得了！$h#$e#I'm gonna stay here to try and keep her calm, though. / 我还是待在这里让她冷静下来吧。",
        "fall_Mon": "So... it's the big harvest season, isn't it? / 那么……收获季到来了，是吧？",
        "breakUp": "... alright...$s / ……好吧……$s#$b#I guess I'll see you around, then...$s / 那，也许……我们就有缘再见吧……$s",
        "AcceptGift_(O)StardropTea": "Hey, thank you. I'll drink this when the sky gets dark. / 哎，谢谢你，等天黑了我就喝。",
        "winter_Sat6": "I like winter but I do feel bad for all the cold animals out there. / 我很喜欢冬天，可每次想到外面受冻的动物们心情就不大好。#$e#I guess they're used to it, though... like me. / 不过它们应该也已经习惯了吧……就像我一样。",
        "Wed2_inlaw_Abigail": "Sam is probably my only friend in this town, anymore... / 山姆也许是我在镇上的唯一朋友。",
        "eventSeen_4081148": "The show went well. I was kind of nervous beforehand, but once we went up on stage I just kinda got into the zone. / 之前的表演很顺利。开始前我有点紧张，但上台之后我就进入状态了。",
        "summer_Tue": "I'm looking forward to the cold, damp season. I feel more at home. / 我比较喜欢阴冷潮湿的季节。那样更有家的感觉。",
        "Sun2": "Having a good weekend? ...nice. / 周末还开心吗？……那就好。",
        "dating_Sebastian": "Don't make fun of me... but I've never been in a relationship like this before.$l / 我从来没有谈过这样的关系……你不要笑我啊。$l^Don't make fun of me... but I've never really had a girlfriend before.$l / 我从来没有交过女朋友……你不要笑我啊。$l",
        "summer_27": "Tomorrow we'll all be gathering at the docks to see the migration of the moonlight jellies. I think it starts at ten o'clock. / 明天我们会在渡口集会，见证月光水母的迁徙。大概十点钟开始。",
        "winter_Tue10": "You came here to see me?$l / 你是来看我的吗？$l#$e#...$h / ……$h",
        "winter_Fri8": "When I was younger I'd run out to the railroad whenever I heard a train coming. / 我小时候，每次听到有火车靠近就会跑到轨道去看。#$e#Whatever happened to those days...? *sigh*$s / 那样的日子哪儿去了呢……？*唉*$s",
        "winter_Sat": "The frogs aren't very happy in winter. / 青蛙们冬天可就不爽了。#$e#Poor little guys.$s||I wonder what the frogs do in winter? Do they just become frozen and then thaw out in spring? / 真是可怜的小家伙。$s||青蛙冬天会干什么？难道就是冻起来，然后春天再解冻？",
        "Sat2": "You know, I should be doing something productive right now. I just lose focus too fast...$s / 话说，还是做一点有意义的事情吧。我总是三分钟热度……$s#$b#Maybe I should drink more coffee? / 也许我该多喝咖啡？",
        "event_city3": "Oh... Well maybe this wasn't the right place to bring you, then. I thought you'd see the beauty in it.$s / 噢……那看来不该带你来这里的。我还以为你会发觉其中的魅力呢。$s",
        "FlowerDance_Accept": "Oh yeah? ... Alright, I will. / 啊？……好吧，可以的。#$b#Heh... maybe this festival isn't so bad.$h / 唔……这个节日好像也没那么糟糕。$h",
        "Resort_Shore": "You think Willy would let me lug a jet ski out here? / 你觉得威利会允许我拖一辆水上摩托出去吗？#$b#...Nah.$h / ……算了。$h",
        "Fri_bad": "Oh yea? Hmm... Not really my thing, but everyone's different I guess.$u / 是吗？嗯……不是我的心头好，但是各花入各眼吧。$u",
        "Thu4": "Why does everyone like Maru so much? Sure, she's smart and friendly, but don't they realize it's all just an attention-grabbing scam? / 为什么所有人都那么喜欢玛鲁？没错，她是聪明又友善，但是难道大家就没发现这只是她吸引注意力的伎俩吗？#$e#Sorry...$s / 抱歉……$s",
        "summer_Sun": "I usually only go outside after dark. Does that sound weird to you? / 我通常只有天黑后才出去。这个你觉得奇怪吗？",
        "AcceptGift_(O)236": "You brought me soup? That's really nice of you.$h / 你给我带了汤？我很喜欢。$h#$b#This one brings back a lot of memories... / 这让我想起了很多往事……",
        "Wed6": "You and Sam are probably my only friends in this town.$s / 你跟山姆是我在这镇上唯一的朋友。$s",
        "Thu8": "$query PLAYER_NPC_RELATIONSHIP current any married roommate#Hey... How are things going on the farm? / $query PLAYER_NPC_RELATIONSHIP current any married roommate#嘿……最近农场怎么样？#$e#Same old routine, huh? Yeah, I know a thing or two about that...|Could you picture me living on a farm? / 每天都是一成不变的日常是不是？我也略有这种感受……|你能想象我这样的人住在农场里吗？#$e#It seems ridiculous, but I have been thinking about it lately. / 虽然很荒唐，但最近我一直在考虑着。",
        "summer_Mountain_58_35": "#$c .5#The temperature only starts to get comfortable at night. / #$c .5#到晚上温度就会变得舒适起来了。#$e#It always seems to stay a little cooler by the lake. / 湖边的气温似乎总是低一些。",
        "fall_Sun": "The sun is coming out less and less these days... wonderful. / 最近太阳越来越少了……好极了。",
        "winter_Thu": "I wonder what's for dinner tonight... *grumble*$s / 不知今晚吃什么呢……*嘟囔*$s",
        "fall_Tue6": "Who does Demetrius think he is, telling me what to do? He's not even my real father.$a / 德米特里厄斯算哪根葱，还对我指手画脚？他又不是我亲爹。$a",
        "fall_Thu": "My room might be a little less depressing if I had a window...$s / 要是房间有窗户的话也许就不那么阴郁了……$s",
        "GreenRain_2": "I was hoping this weather would come back. It makes me appreciate the summer a little more. / 我之前一直希望这种天气再来一次，会让我对夏天更有盼头。",
        "winter_Wed": "%Sebastian seems lost in thought... / %塞巴斯蒂安好像陷入了沉思……",
        "Resort": "The beach is nice, but I don't love the crowds. / 海滩不错，但我不喜欢人多的地方。",
        "secondChance_Guys": "Hey... / 嘿……",
        "summer_Mon6": "Everyone is so happy when it's sunny out... / 外面太阳高照的时候大家都很开心……#$e#Different people like different things, I guess.||Most people like the sun, huh? / 看来是萝卜白菜各有所爱吧。||大部分人都喜欢太阳吧？#$b#I guess you do need a minimum amount of vitamin D... / 人大概还是需要最低限度的维生素D的……",
        "event_garage3": "Don't worry, I'll make sure to show you the ropes before I let you do anything dangerous.$8 / 不用担心，放你去做危险的事之前我会先好好指导你的。$8^There's no need to worry... I'll make sure you're safe.$8 / 不用担心……我会确保你的安全的。$8",
        "summer_Wed10": "Why am I grinning? I guess I've been unusually happy lately...$l / 我为什么在笑？感觉我最近一直很开心，真奇怪……$l",
        "dumped_Guys": "I don't want to see you for a while.$u / 在一段时间里，我不想见到你。$u",
        "firstVisit_Railroad": "I'm glad the path to the railroad tracks is open again. / 又能到铁路那里去了，我很开心。#$b#I like going up there when I feel like being alone. / 我有的时候想要独处，就喜欢到那里去。#$e#...Which is often. / ……不是有的时候，是经常。",
        "winter_Tue6": "I was so close to screaming at Mom for throwing away my old comic collection... But something stopped me. / 我妈把我的漫画收藏扔掉的时候，我差一点就对她大吼起来……但不知怎么就没喊出来。#$e#Hmm... with age comes wisdom. / 嗯……果然年龄带来智慧啊。",
        "winter_Tue": "Hmm... I don't really have anything to say. I still don't know you very well. / 嗯……我还真想不出什么可说的。我跟你还不大熟。",
        "winter_Tue4": "Hey... / 嘿……#$b#It's hard to think of new things to talk about, sometimes. Even after you know someone. / 有时候很难想到新的聊天话题。就算是熟人也一样。#$e#...Sorry. / ……抱歉。",
        "fall_Tue10": "I've always felt like an underdog. But the challenge will just make me stronger. / 我一直感觉人生很失败，但是挑战会让我变得更强大。",
        "Sun": "Hey. Your name is @, right? / 嘿。你叫@，对吧？",
        "winter_Wed4": "Hey, don't let me stop you from getting your work done. / 喂，要是我碍事了你可得告诉我啊。#$e#If you aren't busy I don't mind if you stick around.$h / 你要是不忙的话我倒可以陪陪你。$h",
        "fall_Wed8": "I'm glad you showed up. I was starting to get bored. / 还好你出现了。我都感觉有点无聊了。#$e#Now I feel a lot more energetic, believe it or not. / 不过现在我觉得精神多了，信不信由你。",
        "winter_Sun6": "I built a snowgoon but Demetrius made me get rid of it... yet Maru's cute little snowman goes unharmed!$a / 我堆了个怪物雪人，德米特里厄斯逼着我拆掉了……而玛鲁那个可爱的小雪人他就不管！$a#$e#Ridiculous. / 真是想不通。",
        "divorced": "Why do you keep bothering me? I'm trying to forget about you.$s / 为什么你还要来烦我？我在努力忘掉你。$s",
        "married_Maru": "Demetrius has been all wound up because of the wedding, it's been pretty tense around the house. / 德米特里厄斯在婚礼前一直很焦虑，搞得家里也很紧张。",
        "Wed10": "I dunno where I'd be without you... probably in a ditch somewhere.$l / 如果没有你的话……我大概还在碌碌无为吧。$l",
        "Sun4": "I usually stay inside, but I do go to the beach now and then. / 我通常会待在家里，但是偶尔也会去沙滩。#$b#Pretty much only when it's raining, though. / 不过都是在雨天时才去。#$e#For some reason, staring off into the bleak horizon makes me feel... I dunno. Like it's worthwhile to keep pushing on, I guess. / 不知为何，遥望天水一线的苍茫让我感觉……我也说不清。让我有动力继续向前走的感觉。",
        "winter_Thu6": "I should learn how to cook. That would be useful. / 我应该学学做饭。一定能派上大用场。",
        "summer_Fri": "Oh, hey. *yawn*... sorry. / 哦，嘿。*哈欠*……不好意思。",
        "event_city1": "Hmm... Not exactly how I'd put it but, yeah. / 嗯……换做我肯定不会这么说，不过说得对。",
        "Event_cave3": "It's too dangerous without a sword. But I like your sense of adventure.$h / 不带把剑就去实在太危险了。不过我很欣赏你的冒险精神。$h",
        "dating_Sebastian_memory_oneday": "Hey... you look great.$l / 哎……你很好看。$l#$e#I've been thinking about you all day...$l / 我一整天都在想你……$l",
        "Tue": "I was thinking... people are like stones skipping over the water. / 我在想……人类就像在水上弹跳的石头。#$b#Eventually we're going to sink. / 最终总会沉入水里。",
        "AcceptBirthdayGift_Negative": "Uhh... well, I appreciate the thought. / 呃……行吧，你的心意我领了。",
        "spring_23": "Ugh... Tomorrow is the worst festival of the year by a mile. Just wait and see how stupid I look during the flower dance. / 呃……明天绝对是全年中最蠢的节日了。等着瞧我在花舞节上的傻样子吧。",
        "FlowerDance_Accept_Spouse": "Ugh... do we have to? Alright. / 呃……我们非得这样做吗？那好吧。",
        "summer_Sun4": "Last night, I saw a group of bats flying around near the lake. / 昨夜，我看到一群蝙蝠在湖边飞过。#$e#I guess maybe they are feeding on the mosquitoes this time of year? / 看来到了他们去吃蚊子的季节了？",
        "Resort_Wander": "...Now, if I were a tropical frog, where would I hide...$h / ……嗯，如果我是一只热带蛙，我会躲在哪……$h",
        "summer_Wed": "What's the point of going outside? I've already seen it all. / 出去转悠有什么意义呢？反正我也什么都看过了。",
        "Resort_Towel": "It's good to get away from the computer and see the real world sometimes. I forget how nice it can be.$h / 有时候，能够离开电脑，看看现实世界是什么模样，还是挺不错的。我快忘了这样的感觉能够有多棒。$h",
        "event_city4": "Ugh... You sound like my Mom.$a / 呃……你怎么跟我妈一个调调。$a#$b#...*sigh*$s / ……*唉*$s#$b#You're right, though. I'm addicted to these things, it's not good.$s / 不过你说得对。我对这些东西很上瘾，这可不妙。$s",
        "Event_game2": "Good choice. That works well with my role. / 真是明智的选择。这和我的角色很相配嘛。",
        "Mon4": "If I just disappeared would it really matter?$s / 要是我突然消失，会有人挂念我吗？$s",
        "fall_Mon4": "You're probably making a lot of money on your farm, huh? / 你的农场一定很赚钱吧？#$e#I guess I should get a job soon...$s / 看来我也要尽快找个工作了……$s",
        "summer_Mon": "Everyone is so happy in the sun. I don't get it. / 大家沉浸在阳光中时都十分快乐的样子。真是搞不懂。",
        "fall_Fri": "*yawn*... I was up until 3 reading this new book...#$q 62/63 fall_Fri_old#Do you read, @?#$r 62 -30 Fri_bad#Yep. The classics.#$r 63 30 Fri_good#Only Sci-fi and Fantasy#$r 62 0 Fri_bad#I like a good Romance#$r 63 -30 Fri_bad#No, I don't read books / *哈欠*……我昨晚看一本书看到三点……#$q 62/63 fall_Fri_old#你平时读书吗，@?#$r 62 -30 Fri_bad#嗯。看些经典名著。#$r 63 30 Fri_good#只看科幻与奇幻作品。#$r 62 0 Fri_bad#我喜欢言情作品。#$r 63 -30 Fri_bad#不，我不看书的。",
        "AcceptGift_(O)Book_Defense": "What are you trying to say... I need to work out?$s / 你这是什么意思……想让我锻炼吗？$s#$b#Well, I'm more of a 'nimble' guy... Maybe I'll read the first half.$h / 唔，我不想变那么壮实……我就随便翻翻看吧。$h",
        "AcceptGift_(O)227": "$c 0.8#I really love this. How did you know?$h#Mmm... once you get used to eating raw fish, it becomes really addictive. / $c 0.8#我超喜欢这个，你怎么知道的？$h#嗯……一旦你习惯了吃生鱼，就会很上瘾。",
        "spring_12": "I'm not too big on festivals. Lots of commotion, too much social interaction... More stress than fun, if you ask me. / 我不怎么喜欢过节。又吵闹，又要忙于社交应酬……与其说是减压，还不如说是困扰。",
        "Sat": "What? I didn't hear you... I'm busy thinking about something. / 什么？我没听清楚你说的话……刚才我在想着一些事。#$e#What do you want? / 您想要什么？",
        "Event_cave1": "Not so fast! I want to know what it is. / 别着急！我想先搞清是什么东西呢。",
        "Fri_good": "Oh yeah? Well, did you read the new 'Cave Saga X'? I won't spoil it for you, but oh man...$h / 是吗？那你看过最新的“山洞冒险故事 X”吗？我不会剧透，但是那剧情可真是……$h",
        "winter_Mon": "I'm enjoying this gloomy weather... although I have to say, it's a little cold. / 我倒是挺喜欢这个阴沉的天气的……不过确实有点冷。",
        "Fri": "Uh... I don't really know you. / 呃……我不是很了解你。",
        "Resort_Leaving": "I'm ready to get back home. / 我已经准备好回家了。",
        "Resort_Bar": "I usually wear black, but in this heat... / 我通常都穿黑衣服，但现在天气这么热……",
        "fall_Fri6": "I've been reading a book about a farmer. Reminds me a lot of you, actually.$h / 我在读一本关于农夫的书。说起来，里面说的东西感觉很像你嘛。$h#$e#Sorry if that creeps you out.$h / 啊，抱歉，说了奇怪的话。$h",
        "fall_Fri_bad": "Huh. Sounds boring. / 嗯。听上去怪无聊的。",
        "event_garage1": "Great.$8 / 非常好。$8"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/Shane",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "Mon6": "I'll be honest, I still can't understand why you'd want to be friends with me.||Life isn't fair, and I can't help but feel bitter about it. / 说实话，我还是不太理解为什么你要和我交朋友。||人生很不公平，我忍不住会产生怨恨。",
        "Fri8": "Buh... Can you imagine how disgusting my liver must look?$s / 唉……我的肝肯定已经糟糕透了吧？$s#$e#My body feels twenty years older than it should...$s / 我感觉身体已经老了二十岁了……$s",
        "Sun10": "Hi, @. I've actually been having a pretty good day so far.$h / 嗨，@。其实今天我过得还挺不错。$h",
        "Resort_Entering": "Buh... hope the bar's open. / 呃……但愿酒吧开着。",
        "Thu": "What do you want? Leave me alone. / 您想要什么？别来烦我。",
        "Sat8": "I've really grown attached to Marnie's chickens.$h||A chicken will never let you down. Humans, on the other hand... / 我和玛妮的鸡建立了很深的感情呢。$h||鸡从来不会让你失望，人类就说不准了……",
        "Thu6": "Buh... Where's the Joja Cola?||Why try? Life's just a roll of the dice. / 呃……哪里有 Joja 可乐？||管他做什么？人生就是骰子掷出来的。#$e#When they rolled mine, the dice fell off the table. / 掷我的骰子的时候，骰子直接从桌子上掉下来了。",
        "event_noLoan3": "Oh, wow...$s / 噢，哇……$s",
        "Mon": "I don't know you. Why are you talking to me? / 我不认识你。你为什么要和我说话啊？",
        "Tue6": "Life isn't so bad... at least I have frozen pizza and eggs.$u / 生活也没那么糟嘛……至少还有冻披萨和鸡蛋可吃。$u",
        "FlowerDance_Decline": "...No.$s / ……不。$s",
        "Mon10": "Do you ever feel like the whole world is scrutinizing you like some disgusting insect? / 你有没有过这种感觉：整个世界都对你充满了恶意？",
        "Wed": "No, I don't have time to chat with you. / 不行，我没时间和你聊天。",
        "Resort_Chair": "Hoo... Feels good to rest these hams. / 呼……总算能让我烤焦的腿休息一下了。#$b#If anyone needs me, I'll just be sitting here, marinating. / 有人找我的话让他来这里，我会一直坐在这儿腌着我的腿。",
        "pamHouseUpgrade": "I heard you built Pam a house... That's really generous... / 我听说你为潘姆建了一间房子……真是慷慨……#$b#You know, I could use a hundred thousand gold myself... / 你知道，我可以给自己花十万金币……#$e#*ahem* ...ah ...Just kidding. ...Heh. / *啊哈*……啊……开玩笑的。……嘿。",
        "event_noLoan2": "Okay, Dad...$s / 好的，爸爸……$s^Okay, Mom...$s / 好的，妈妈……$s",
        "event_noLoan1": "I didn't know you were such a miser...$s / 我不知道你是这样一个守财奴……$s",
        "Tue8": "We should go to a Tunnelers game some time. When I go by myself, I usually drink way too much beer. / 我们哪天一起去看隧道队的比赛呗，我一个人去总是会喝太多。",
        "GreenRain": "I don't have to go into work today, so I'm not complaining... / 今天不用去上班了，所以我没什么怨言……",
        "breakUp": "*gulp* Oh... Yeah, okay... I guess I should've seen this coming.$s / （咽口水）哦……嗯，好吧……我早该知道会变成这样的。$s#$b#I'll... uh... guess I'll see you at the Saloon. / 我……呃……那就餐吧见。",
        "AcceptGift_(O)StardropTea": "Heh... thanks. Tastes just like beer. / 哦……谢了。味道跟啤酒差不多嘛。",
        "Tue4": "Every time I try something new it goes horribly wrong. You learn to just stay in a shell. / 每次我做出什么新尝试时都会闯祸。后来就慢慢学着安于现状了。",
        "Sun2": "You again? How many times do I have to tell you to leave me alone?$s / 又是你？跟你说过多少次了，别来烦我！$s",
        "Sat2": "#$1 ShaneJOSH#I'm surprised that you're still trying to make friends with me. Haven't I been rude enough to you yet? / #$1 ShaneJOSH#你居然还想和我交朋友，真是太奇怪了。我对你难道还不够粗鲁吗？#$e#*sigh*...$s / *唉*……$s",
        "Sun6": "...I think I might be gaining weight.$s / ……我最近好像变胖了。$s",
        "FlowerDance_Accept": "Um... sure. / 呃……好啊。#$e#I'd better stop eating... / 我还是别再吃了……",
        "Resort_Shore": "That's right... I'm not wearing any shoes or socks. / 没错……我不穿鞋子也不穿袜子。#$b#Some call it a public health risk. / 有人说这是公共卫生的潜在风险。#$b#The crabs seem to enjoy it, though.$h / 但螃蟹们似乎很喜欢。$h",
        "Mon2": "I hardly know you. Why are you talking to me?||What's the point of talking to me? I don't want any friends. / 我和你完全不熟。你为什么要和我说话？||跟我说话做什么？我不想交朋友。",
        "Thu4": "You're really persistent. I guess I'm just surprised that anyone would be interested in talking to me. / 你还真是锲而不舍。我们真没想到，竟还有人愿意和我说话。",
        "Sat4": "$d Joja#I'm renting my room from Marnie at a really good price. It's small but I can't complain. / 我的房间是从玛妮手里租的，价格实惠。虽然很小，不过我也知足了。|If I could reset my life maybe I'd start a chicken farm. Only free-range eggs of course. / 要是我能从头来过，也许我会经营一家养鸡场呢。当然只卖散养鸡蛋。",
        "Thu8": "You like talking to me? I guess I believe you... maybe you're as weird as I am.$h / 你喜欢跟我说话吗？我大概是信了……也许你和我一样奇怪。$h",
        "Tue10": "I need to keep it together for Jas' sake. I don't want to be a bad role model for her.||I'm kind of like a father figure to Jas. I just hope I haven't let her down too much.$s / 为了贾斯，我怎么说都要控制住自己。我不想成为她的坏榜样。||我对贾斯毕竟还算是一个父亲的身份，但愿她没有对我太失望。$s",
        "Sat10": "Your farm seems like a great place to raise chickens.$h / 你的农场看起来很适合养鸡。$h",
        "event_apologize2": "I know... that's why I stopped by, to tell you about it. / 我知道……这就是为什么我停下来，告诉你这个。",
        "AcceptBirthdayGift_Loved": "Oh, is it my birthday? I was hoping I'd forget. / 啊，今天是我生日吗？我都快忘了呢。#$b#This is actually really nice, though. Thank you.$h / 我真的很喜欢这个。谢谢你。$h",
        "eventSeen_3910975": "Sorry you had to see me like that, @...$s / @，让你看到我那副样子实在抱歉……$s",
        "GreenRain_2": "Oh, there's some kind of weird weather today? I didn't notice. / 啊，今天天气很奇怪吗？我没注意。",
        "event_room1": "Okay... that'll require a great script. Maybe I'll ask Elliott for advice next time I see him at the saloon.$s / 嗯……这可得有个好剧本才行。也许下次再在酒吧见到艾利欧特的时候，向他请教下吧。$s",
        "Tue2": "What do you want from me? Money? I'd give you a pot of gold to leave me alone! / 你找我到底要干什么啊？要钱？要是你不来烦我，我给你一大桶金子都乐意！",
        "Resort": "Okay, this sand is piping hot. I regret not wearing shoes.$s / 行吧，这里的沙子真烫。我后悔没穿鞋了。$s",
        "event_stadium1": "Oh yeah? I guess that makes sense.$6 / 哦，是吗？也有些道理。$6#$b#Me? I get bored with Pelican Town sometimes. / 我？我有时会厌烦鹈鹕镇。#$b#But... I like that you're different. We balance each other out.$l / 但是……我喜欢与众不同的你。我们两个刚好互补。$l",
        "secondChance_Guys": "I don't understand you... *sigh*... / 我不明白你……*叹*",
        "AcceptGift_(O)203": "Oh, you made it? *squish*... Um... *smack*... I think I'll stick to frozen pizza. But thanks. / 哦，这是你做的？（捏）……呃……（啪）……我觉得我还是吃冷冻披萨吧。谢谢你。",
        "Wed8": "I guess I've grown attached to Marnie and Jas. We're a ragtag bunch but it kind of feels like a weird family. / 看来我是和玛妮和贾斯有了感情呢。我们都是身份卑微的人，却有一种微妙的家庭感。#$e#I never really had much of a family as a kid.$s / 我小时候并没有家。$s",
        "dating_Shane_memory_oneday": "I think I might be the luckiest guy in the world... $h / 我可能是世界上最幸运的人了……$h",
        "eventSeen_611944_memory_oneweek": "Have you tried the new Joja Bubblerito? I ate two in one sitting yesterday, that was a mistake... / 新出的 Joja 泡泡玉米煎饼你尝过了没？我昨天连吃了两个，结果很后悔……",
        "Fri10": "My body hurts a lot less since I cut back on the booze. / 自从我开始减少喝酒，身体就没那么疼了。#$e#But it still feels like I'm always teetering on the edge...$s / 但我感觉还是一直在危险的边缘……$s",
        "Sun": "I'm busy, can't you tell?||...I don't feel like talking to anyone. / 我忙着呢，你看不出来吗？||……我现在不想跟人说话。",
        "divorced": "...$a / ……$a#$e#...Leave me alone.$a / ……离我远点。$a",
        "Fri6": "I'll definitely be going to the saloon tonight. What else is there to do? / 我今晚绝对要去酒吧。还有什么别的事可做呢？",
        "Sun4": "Hmm... it's %time. Should I throw a frozen pizza in the microwave, or should I wait?$u||If the Tunnelers win, I'll knock back a cold one to celebrate. / 嗯……现在是%time。我是往微波炉里扔个冷冻披萨呢，还是继续等？$u||如果隧道队赢了，我就来一瓶冰啤酒庆祝一下。#$e#If they lose? I'll have a cold one to drown my sorrows. / 如果输了？那我就喝一瓶冰啤酒来消愁。",
        "Sun8": "If I watch more TV maybe I can forget about life. That would be relaxing.$u / 要是我再多看些电视，应该就能忘掉生活中的烦心事了吧。那可就太棒了。$u",
        "event_room2": "Sounds great. I'll have to create a bunch of practical effects to make it look cool. / 听上去不错嘛。我去搞点特效什么的，看起来会更炫酷。",
        "event_stadium2": "Oh really? I'm surprised... Didn't you move to Stardew Valley to escape the noise of the city?$6 / 真的吗？我很惊讶……你搬到星露谷不就是为了逃离城市的喧嚣吗？$6#$b#I mean... Don't get me wrong, I totally understand. My life in Pelican Town is pretty bland, you know. / 我的意思是……别误会我的意思，我完全理解。我在鹈鹕镇的生活是相当乏味，你知道的。",
        "Fri4": "$d Joja#What's the point of life if all you do is work? / 要是成天工作，人生还有什么意义？|I haven't been able to pay my rent, but Marnie's letting me stay anyway. I'm lucky. / 我连房租都付不起，不过玛妮还是没赶我走。真是交了好运。",
        "dating_Shane": "I... wasn't really expecting this, after all I've put you through... / 我……我没想到之前对你那样，你还会不计前嫌……",
        "Tue": "What? What do you want? Go away. / 什么？您想要什么？快走开。",
        "JojaMart": "%Shane's hard at work. He doesn't seem interested in talking. / %谢恩正在努力工作。似乎没兴趣聊天。",
        "FlowerDance_Accept_Spouse": "Dance? Hoo-boy. Okay... let me chug a few more of these first... / 跳舞？好呀。等我一下，我先多吃几个……",
        "Mon4": "Hey. Sorry if I came off as rude when we first met. / 嘿。如果你觉得我们初次相见时我太粗鲁的话，我道歉。#$e#It takes me a while to warm up to strangers.||It's a lot of effort to be friends with someone. It's easier to just be alone. / 我这人比较认生。||跟别人交朋友要花很多精力，还是一个人比较轻松。",
        "event_apologize1": "...Yeah, me too. / ……是的，我也是。",
        "eventSeen_3910975_memory_oneweek": "I'm trying to cut back on the drinks... it's not going to be easy. / 我在努力少喝酒了……但是感觉不会很轻松。",
        "Wed4": "$d Joja#*sigh* ...Every day is the same. Stocking those horrible shelves, going to the saloon, tossing and turning all night.$s / *唉*……每天都是一样，给恶心的货架摆货，去酒吧，然后一夜辗转难眠。$s|I hated my job at JojaMart, but now that I'm unemployed I feel even worse. / 我讨厌原来在 Joja 超市的工作，但现在失业了，感觉就更糟了。$s",
        "AcceptBirthdayGift_Liked": "Oh, is it my birthday? That's right... I almost forgot. Thanks. / 啊，今天是我生日吗？对哦……我差点忘了。谢谢你。",
        "pamHouseUpgradeAnonymous": "I heard someone bought Pam a house... *sigh*... What did Pam ever do to earn that kind of generosity?? / 我听说有人给潘姆买了一间房子……*叹*潘姆曾经做过什么，才能换来如此慷慨？",
        "Sat": "Why are you bothering me? I want to be alone. / 你为什么要来烦我？我想清静清静。",
        "Fri": "Don't you have work to do? / 你没活干吗？",
        "Resort_Leaving": "Welp... got my year's supply of Vitamin D. Now I can play video games with the blinds shut the rest of the year. / 啊……我一年的维他命 D 摄入量已经满了，所以今年剩下的时间里，我可以暗无天日地打游戏了。",
        "event_apologize3": "Wow, it was that serious, huh? I can hardly remember... / 哇，有那么严重吗？我都快记不清了……",
        "Resort_Bar": "Phew... feels good to have a cold drink... / 呼……喝冷饮的感觉真不错……#$e#Or maybe a few... / 要不再来点……",
        "dumped_Guys": "%Shane has a glazed look in his eye. He won't speak to you. / %谢恩的眼中闪闪发光。他不会跟你说话。"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/Vincent",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "GreenRain_2": "%Vincent is covered in moss. / %文森特全身都是苔藓。",
        "GreenRain": "Mom! I wanna go outside and play!%noturn / 妈妈！我想出去玩！%noturn",
        "Sat_1": "Dad's coming back soon! / 爸爸就要回来啦！#$b#I hope he brings me some toys.$u / 不知他有没有给我买玩具回来呢。$u",
        "Sun10": "Hi Uncle @! / 你好啊，@叔叔！^Hi Auntie @! / 嗨，@姑妈！#$e#Don't tell Mom... but you're my favorite grown-up.$h / 别告诉我妈……不过大人里面我最喜欢你了。$h",
        "Resort_Entering": "That was fun! I wanna be a boat captain some day! / 真好玩！以后我想当个船长！",
        "Resort": "If you look close, you can see little bugs jumping out of the sand.$h / 如果凑近了看，你就能看到沙子里有小虫子跳出来。$h",
        "Thu2": "You're not as boring as most grown-ups! / 你不像大多数大人们那么无聊呢！",
        "Thu": "I'm hungry... where's Mom?$s / 好饿啊……妈妈呢？$s",
        "Tue": "*sigh*... Mom won't let me have any more gummies today.$s / *唉*……妈妈今天不让我再多吃软糖了。$s",
        "AcceptGift_(O)StardropTea": "Wow! It's so sweet! Mmmmm.... / 哇！好甜！唔……",
        "AcceptBirthdayGift_Negative": "A birthday present? Oh... this isn't very fun.$s / 是生日礼物吗？啊……好像没什么意思。$s",
        "Sat8": "$d kent#Dad seems weird since he came back. I wonder what happened to him?$s / 爸爸回来之后似乎变了很多。不知出了什么事呢？$s#$b#He doesn't play with me anymore.$s / 他都不和我玩了。$s|I wonder if Dad will ever come home... / 我想知道爸爸是否还会回家……$s",
        "Introduction": "Oh, a stranger! My name's Vincent. / 哦，陌生人啊！我叫文森特。#$b#Momma says not to talk to strangers... But you seem okay. / 妈妈跟我说不要和陌生人说话……但你看来是个好人。",
        "reject_869": "Oooh! Nice find! / 噢噢噢！不错的发现！#$b#Mom wouldn't let me keep him, though...$s / 但是，妈妈不会让我留下他的……$s",
        "Mon": "I wanna be just like my big brother when I grow up!$h / 等我长大了，我也要像哥哥一样！$h#$e#Okay! Bye! / 好的！再见。",
        "Tue6": "Can you keep a secret, mister? / 你能为我保守个秘密吗，先生？^Can you keep a secret, miss?$u / 你能为我保守个秘密吗，女士？$u#$b#I wanna marry Miss Penny when I grow up. / 我长大后想娶潘妮小姐为妻。#$e#Just don't tell her, okay?$u / 不要告诉她，好吗？$u",
        "Resort_Shore": "I wanna see a shark!$h / 我想看鲨鱼！$h",
        "Mon4": "$d kent#I'm glad Dad's back... but he's different than I remember...$s / 我很高兴爸爸回来了……但已经和我记忆中不同了……$s|Dad's not around much... I miss playing with him. / 爸爸总是不在家……好想和他一起玩。$s",
        "AcceptGift_Negative_alcohol_item": "*sniff*... what is this? It smells awful... Mommmm!!!$s / （闻了一下）……这是什么？好难闻……妈妈！！！$s",
        "Sun": "Hi there, mister! / 你好啊，先生！^Hi there, miss. / 你好啊，女士。",
        "Wed": "I wanna look for bugs, but Mom gets mad when I'm all dirty.$u / 我想去捉虫子，但每次搞得脏兮兮又会被妈妈骂。$u#$b#It's a tough choice. / 真是艰难的抉择啊。",
        "Sat": "Miss Penny makes me read a new book every week.$s / 潘妮小姐每周都要求我读一本新书。$s#$b#At least she lets me pick them, sometimes! / 至少有时候她还会让我来选书！",
        "AcceptBirthdayGift_Positive": "Is that a birthday present? Can I open it now? / 是给我的生日礼物吗？我能现在就拆开吗？#$b#Oh, wow! This is exactly what I wanted! Yayayaya!$h / 哇！我正好想要这个！好耶！$h",
        "Fri": "#$c .3#Ew, it's boiled beet night again...$s / #$c .3#呃，又是煮甜菜……$s#$e#Oh no... Mom's making lentil soup tonight.$s / 糟了……我妈今晚会做扁豆汤。$s",
        "Resort_Leaving": "I wanna come back soon! / 真想早点再来玩！",
        "AcceptGift_(TR)FrogEgg": "*Squish* *squish* ... Ewww! Can I have it? Can I have it? Yaaay!$h / （捏了两下）……好恶心！能给我吗？快给我吧？好耶！$h",
        "married_Sam": "Don't take my Sammy away!$s / 不许抢走我的山姆哥哥！$s"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/Willy",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "GreenRain_2": "If the fish like these rains, then I like 'em, too. / 如果鱼喜欢这场雨，那我也喜欢。",
        "Sun10": "Hey, it's my skipper, @!$h / 哎呀呀，这不是@船长嘛！$h#$e#I'd give you a discount on bait if I could afford it.$s / 要是我能承受得起，我就给你的鱼饵打个折。$s",
        "winter_12": "Don't give up just yet! There's more squid in these waters... / 继续加把劲！水里还有好多鱿鱼嘞……",
        "Thu2": "There's rumors of some very rare fish in these parts... but only an experienced angler could stand a chance against them. / 据说这一片水域有很稀有的鱼出现呢……但是只有经验很丰富的钓者才有可能战胜他们。#$e#You'll need the finest bait you can get if you want a rare fish to bite. / 想要让稀有的鱼咬钩，得要用最好的鱼饵才行。",
        "Thu": "*mumble* *mumble* ...Eh? I would tell you about my thoughts, but it's a fisherman's secret. / *嘟嘟**囔囔*……什么？我其实挺想把我的想法跟你说说，但都是些渔夫的秘密。",
        "Sat8": "How's the fishing life going for ya? / 鱼钓的怎么样啊？#$e#I try to fish as often as possible, but it's not easy when you've got a shop to run. / 我一有机会就去钓鱼，但还有个商店要打理，所以机会并不多啊。",
        "Introduction": "Ahoy there! It's nice to see young folk movin' in to the valley. It's not very common these days. / 你好呀！看到有年轻人搬进谷里真是太高兴了。这个年代这种事可不多见了。",
        "fishCaught_682": "*sniff* *sniff*... Something tells me you've been fishin' in the sewers, lad. / （闻了两下）……小伙子，你是不是在下水道钓鱼了？^*sniff* *sniff*... Something tells me you've been fishin' in the sewers, miss. / （闻了两下）……小姑娘，你是不是在下水道钓鱼了？#$b#It's an unconventional approach, to be sure. There's legend of gargantuan carp, twisted into monsters from the toxic sludge... / 这个办法倒是别出心裁。传说中还有一条被有毒淤泥搞变异的巨大鲤鱼……",
        "Fair_Judging": "I don't have high hopes of winning... the fish look nice but they don't exactly smell great...$s / 我没对获奖寄予厚望……鱼看起来不错，但味道不太好……$s",
        "Mon": "Ahoy there, son. / 你好啊，孩子。^Ahoy there, lass. / 你好啊，小姑娘。#$b#Looks like decent weather for fishing, eh? / 今天天气很适合钓鱼嘛，是不是？",
        "Tue6": "The ol' Man was a fisherman, you know. I grew up sailing between the fern islands, living from catch to catch. / 我这个老头子可是个资深渔夫，知道不。我从小就在各个岛屿之间航行，渐渐长大。#$e#The fishing life is tough, but there's something about it that keeps you goin'. / 渔夫的生活十分艰难，但却有着神奇的魅力。",
        "MovieInvitation": "Ah... a movie. That's kind of ye, lad. / 啊……电影。小伙子，你人真好。^Ah... a movie. That's kind of ye, miss. / 啊……电影。小姑娘，你人真好。#$b#I'll just finish me pipe, and head over. / 等抽完这斗烟，我就过去。",
        "GreenRainFinished": "Well, the fish seem as healthy as ever. In fact, I swear they've been biting with extra vigor! / 鱼好像没事，我甚至觉得它们咬钩更有劲嘞！",
        "Sun": "If you purchase a high quality fishing rod, you'll be able to attach bait and tackle to the line. / 如果购买高级鱼竿，你就可以在鱼线上挂上鱼饵和钓具。#$b#Bait causes fish to bite faster. Tackle can make your job a lot easier when reeling fish in. / 鱼饵可以让鱼儿更快咬钩。钓具则可以让收线过程更轻松。#$e#There's all kinds of tackle, with different perks. They're usually a little flimsy, so don't be surprised if your tackle breaks after a while. / 钓具也有很多种，各有各的优点。这些东西都比较脆弱，所以如果使用了一阵后钓具坏掉了，请不要惊讶。",
        "Wed": "Some fish come and go with the seasons. Others only come out at night or in the rain. / 有些鱼会随着季节变化出现或消失，也有些鱼只会在下雨时或者夜间才会出现。",
        "married": "Giving up the ${bachelor^single}$ life, eh? / 哦，你脱单了啊？#$b#Just don't forget to make time for fishing... / 不过别把钓鱼荒废了……",
        "fishCaught_159": "So, you finally conquered the Crimsonfish! That fish has been taunting me for many years. He nearly nibbled through the wood under me house! / 哦，你终于征服绯红鱼了！几年了，那鱼一直在嘲讽我，就差咬穿地板追到我家来了！",
        "AcceptGift_(O)Book_Roe": "Thank ye! This'll be perfect winter reading. Ah, and it even smells of the sea...$h / 谢谢喽！冬天看这个正合适。哎呀，甚至还有大海的味道……$h",
        "summer_19": "Tomorrow is the annual Trout Derby... Aye, it's a freshwater enthusiast's dream! / 明天就是一年一度的鳟鱼大赛……好哇，爱钓淡水鱼的人要大显身手嘞！#$e#Anglers from all over the world will be here to catch our beautiful Rainbow Trout... / 世界各地的钓鱼高手都会来这里钓虹鳟鱼……#$e#I'd better see you out there, lad!$h / 小伙子，到时候见！$h^I hope to see you out there!$h / 到时候见！$h#$e#For the next two days, I'll only be manning the shop for one hour, starting at 9am. So if you really need somethin', you can come by then. / 后面两天，我只开一个小时的店，从早上 9 点开始。如果你想要买东西的话，要抓紧时间。",
        "Fri4": "I'm a simple man... when my pipe is full, I'm happy. When my pipe is empty... well, then I just fill 'er up again.$u / 我这人很容易满足……烟斗满了我就开心，烟斗空了……嗯，我就再把它塞满。$u",
        "summer_20": "It's the big day! I've got all me equipment tuned to catch Trout... / 今天比赛就开始了！我已经整装待发，要去钓鳟鱼嘞……#$e#Good luck out there! / 祝你好运！",
        "GreenRain": "Aye... I hope these weird rains don't bother the fish... It could ruin me life! / 嗐……但愿鱼群不会受到这场奇怪的雨的影响……不然我可就麻烦喽！",
        "fishCaught_775": "Ah, so you finally snagged the Glacierfish... That's one of the slipperiest fish I've ever encountered! / 啊，你终于逮到冰川鱼了……这可是我见过的最滑头的鱼！#$e#How many tries did it take ya? / 你试了多少次？",
        "Tue": "A true angler has respect for the water... don't you forget that. / 真正的钓者必须懂得尊重水……这一点可不要忘了。",
        "AcceptGift_(O)StardropTea": "By the stem o' me pipe...  a cup o' Stardrop Tea! And here I thought it was only the stuff of mermaid legend. Thank you kindly. / 星之果茶！我烟斗都要掉了……我还以为这是美人鱼传说里的东西嘞。谢谢你啊。",
        "AcceptGift_(O)682": "The horror! ...What kind of monster is this? / 太可怕了！……这是什么怪物？",
        "winter_11": "Tomorrow, at the beach, is the start of a little gathering... called 'SquidFest'. / 明天在海滩上会开始一个小活动……叫做“鱿鱼节”。#$e#Aye... tis' a difficult catch, the squid. But I trust that you've developed a knack for the sport, by now. / 嗐……是挺难钓的，那群鱿鱼，不过你现在肯定已经轻车熟路了。",
        "AcceptGift_Positive_coffee_item": "Ah, this stuff warms the ol' bones. Thank you. / 啊，喝了这个让我这把老骨头暖洋洋的。谢谢你。",
        "AcceptGift_(O)SkillBook_1": "Ah, 'Bait And Bobber'... Every angler ought to have a subscription, but it costs a pretty penny. Taught me a lot of good fishin' tips over the years. Thanks!$h / 啊，《鱼饵和浮漂》……喜欢钓鱼的都应该订一本，我看了这么多年，学会了很多钓鱼技巧，就是定价有点贵。谢谢你！$h",
        "AcceptGift_(O)336": "*chomp*... Yep, that's real gold alright. Heh! What a gift!$h / （咬了一下）……不错，是真金。嗐！谢谢你！$h",
        "FullCrabPond": "*sniff*... Ah... That old familiar scent. You've been raisin' crabs, haven't ya? / （嗅）……啊……那熟悉的味道。你有在饲养螃蟹，是吧？#$b#Yer a ${man^lady}$ after me own heart, @. Hah!$h / 你跟我臭味相投啊，@。哈！$h#$b#Here, take this. I found it on the beach... Been savin' it fer a special occasion. It's not every day I discover a fellow crab enthusiast! [797] / 来，这个拿去。我在沙滩上找到的……我一直留着万一碰到特别情况。我可不是每天都能找到个跟我一样的螃蟹爱好者！[797]",
        "Mon4": "Have you had much luck in the local waters? You look like you could be a strong angler if you set your mind to it. / 你在本地水域有什么收获吗？看你的样子，如果勤加锻炼一定会成为出色的钓手哦。",
        "AcceptGift_(O)Book_Crabbing": "Aye...  A timeless classic. Brings a tear to me eye, with every read. A fisherman can never have too many copies! Thank ye.$h / 好哇……经典永不过时，我每次看都会眼眶湿润。作为渔夫，收藏多少本都不够！谢谢嘞。$h",
        "fishCaught_160": "Ah, you caught the Angler, did ya? A good 'first step' into the world o' rare fish, that one. / 哦，你钓到鮟鱇鱼了啊？那么钓稀有鱼你算是入门了。",
        "accept_869": "Ah... That's the perfect bait for a catfish I've been tryin' to catch! / 啊……我一直都想抓一条鲶鱼，这就是最完美的鱼饵！#$b#Here, let me trade you this for it. I'm not sure what it is, but it washed up on the beach not too long ago. / 来吧，我用这个东西与你交换。我不知道这是什么，但它是在不久前才被冲到海滩上的。#$b#Somethin' tells me you could use it, lad. / 我有种感觉，你会用上它的，小伙子。^Somethin' tells me you could use it, miss. / 我有种感觉，你会用上它的，小姑娘。",
        "summer_21": "How's the Derby treatin' ya so far? / 你比赛的情况怎么样？#$b#I've found plenty o' Golden Tags, meself... but it's not over yet! / 我已经拿到不少黄金标签了……但是还要继续！",
        "fishCaught_163": "By the stem o' me pipe... You actually caught 'the Legend'. I never thought I'd see the day...$h / 谢天谢地……你竟然钓到“传奇之鱼”了，我没想到能在有生之年看到……$h#$b#Well, lad, you've done it... You're the best fisherman this valley's seen in a long time...$h / 嗯，小伙子，你成功了……你是星露谷难得一见的钓鱼好手……$h^Well, miss, you've done it... You're the best angler this valley's seen in a long time...$h / 嗯，小姑娘，你成功了……你是星露谷难得一见的钓鱼好手……$h",
        "winter_13": "It warms me ol' winter heart to see all these anglers gathered here, all for the love o' fishing...$h / 这么多钓鱼好手因为喜欢钓鱼聚集在这里，我真是特别舒心……$h",
        "Wed6": "I've heard a rumor that a special kind of fish can be found in the pools between waterfalls... / 我听传闻说瀑布之间的水塘里有一种特殊的鱼……#$b#If you can reach it with yer rod, that is... / 前提是你用鱼竿能够到那里……",
        "Sat": "If the local fishing scene got a bit more lively, I might expand the shop's stock. / 如果本地的垂钓事业能够更蓬勃一些，也许我会考虑引进新货。",
        "Fri": "If you really want to get the fish biting, make sure you put some bait on your hook. / 如果想让鱼咬钩，可别忘了在钩子上放鱼饵哦。",
        "Fair_Judged": "Wow, I got a low score. I guess Mayor Lewis isn't much of a fish man. Oh well...$s / 哇，我的分数好低。估计是因为镇长刘易斯不喜欢钓鱼。呃……$s"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/Wizard",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "GreenRain_2": "Nature is a powerful force, not to be trifled with. / 自然的力量极为强大，不容小觑。#$e#Excuse me, but there are special matters I can only attend to on this day. / 不好意思，有些特殊的事情我得在今天处理掉。",
        "GreenRain": "Though the unusual rains may be alarming, there is nothing to fear on this day. / 今天反常的雨水可能会令人恐慌，不过其实没什么好怕的。#$e#In fact, it is a day of great joy for many living things. / 很多生物反而高兴还来不及呢。",
        "roommates_Krobus": "It will be a challenge, to live with one such as Krobus. But richly rewarding to both parties, I'm sure. / 和科罗布斯这类生物一起生活是一种考验，不过肯定对双方都很有价值。#$e#I admit, I am most interested to see the outcome of such an unusual friendship. / 这种不寻常的友谊最终结果会如何，我承认我很感兴趣。",
        "Thu": "There are many mysteries around us. You must be patient if you wish to discover them. / 我们周遭有无数神秘的存在。想要发现它们就必须要有足够的耐心……",
        "Tue": "If you have nothing important to tell me, leave me be. I have much work to do. / 如果没有重要的事，请不要打搅我。我还有好多活要干呢。",
        "AcceptGift_(O)StardropTea": "Ah, what do we have here? A rare and potent elixir, it seems. Yes, this will make a fine addition to my reagent chest. / 啊，这是什么好东西？好像是一种罕见的强力药水。很好，我的试剂箱里又新添一个宝贝。",
        "accept_868": "Ah... an arctic shard. / 啊……是极寒碎片。#$b#A most powerful substance, indeed, and potently infused with the element of ice. / 确实，这是最为强大的一种物质，含有强力的冰元素。#$b#I'll take it, if you don't mind. / 如果你不介意的话，我就收下了。#$b#... / ……#$b#...Erm...You're still here. Oh. You want something? / ……呃……你还没走啊。哦。你是想要点什么吗？#$b#...Take this. / ……给你这个。",
        "Tue4": "I trust you enough to allow you in my basement. Treat what you find there with respect. / 我对你的信任足够我放你进地下室了。不过你在下面可不要乱动东西。",
        "Introduction": "Ah, yes. I have predicted your arrival a long time ago, young @. / 啊，没错。我很久前就预见到你的到来了，年轻的@。#$e#However, your fate is ultimately in your own hands. / 不过，你的命运最终还是掌握在你自己手中。",
        "Sat6": "While the scientific practice may accurately describe the material of our world, it will never explain the deepest mysteries... / 虽然科学实践可以精确刻画世界上的物质，但是它永远无法解释最深层的奥秘……",
        "Mon": "Ah, yes. I have seen many things about your future, young @. / 关于你的未来，我看到了很多事啊，年轻的@。#$e#If I were to tell you, there could be grave consequences. / 如果我告诉了你，可能会产生很严重的报应啊。",
        "Sat2": "Have you made any headway with the forest spirits? / 你和森林里的精灵取得什么进展了吗？",
        "MovieInvitation": "Hmm... I suppose I could accompany you... yes. Once you've arrived, I shall appear. Farewell. / 唔……我想我应该能与你作伴……行。等你到了，我便会现身。再会。",
        "Thu10": "You musn't tell anyone... but I have reason to believe that one of the locals is actually my daughter... / 不要告诉别人……但我发现，本地居民中似乎有个人是我的女儿……#$e#I could be mistaken... It's rare, but it does happen. / 也许是我搞错了……虽说这不寻常，却也不是全无可能。",
        "Mon4": "Outside the domain of human civilization is where nature truly reveals its secrets. / 在远离人类文明的地方，大自然才会展现其奥秘。",
        "Sun": "I sometimes observe the local villagers in secret. / 有时我会偷偷观察村民们。#$e#I am hoping to find an apprentice. Some day I will leave this mortal plane, but my arcane pursuits must continue. / 我想找一个人来当我的学徒。终有一天我会离开这具躯壳，但我对于奥术的研究一定要传承下去。",
        "Wed": "It takes years of study to understand the language of the elementals. / 要研究许多年才能理解元素的语言。#$e#To actually speak their language requires a lifetime of devoted effort. / 要想用他们的语言讲话则需要认真研究一辈子才行。#$e#Now, if you'll excuse me... / 那么，抱歉，我要开工了……",
        "Fri6": "I was married, long ago. After my wife and I split, she began flying around the countryside, cursing everything she saw. / 我很久以前结过婚。后来我们分开了，她就在城镇周围四处乱飞，对所见之物下诅咒。#$e#It's not a very mature way to express one's anger. / 用这方法来发泄自己的愤怒，真是孩子气。",
        "Sat": "Beware, you are standing above a potent magical field. / 小心啊，你现在站的地方拥有浓厚的魔力。#$e#I built my hut right here on purpose, you know. / 我把我的屋子建在这里可是有原因的。",
        "Tue10": "If reality is constructed by the mind, then if one were to master the power of mind, they could control reality... / 假如现实是由意识产生的，那么一个人若是掌握了精神的力量，就可以支配现实……",
        "Mon8": "There are areas of the world, yet unsullied by the constraints of modern thinking, where magic is still very much alive... / 世界上还有些地方尚未受到现代思维的桎梏，魔法在那里欣欣向荣……",
        "Fri": "I believe the townsfolk are afraid of me. / 我觉得镇上的人都怕我。#$e#It is unfortunate, but I suppose it is human to be afraid of the unknown. / 虽然很不幸，不过人类惧怕未知也是正常的吧。",
        "married": "Marriage... hmm? I pray that you have better luck than I did... / 唔……结婚？我祈祷你运气会比我当初好吧……",
        "Tue8": "Greetings, @. I trust you haven't been dabbling in the dark arts? / @，你好。我相信你还没有涉足黑魔法吧？"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/MarriageDialogue",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "spring_8": "Now that winter's over, we've got lots of productive weather to look forward to. / 冬天过去了，希望今年能风调雨顺呢。",
        "Good_9": "Oh, I'm not bored... I'm just enjoying what we have here. / 哦，我并不无聊……我只是享受我们所拥有的一切。#$e#It's a simple life, but I like it.$h / 生活虽朴素，但我很喜欢。$h",
        "Bad_2": "Are you still happy with me?$s / 你和我在一起还幸福吗？$s",
        "Rainy_Day_Leah": "Might want to do some fishing or mining today, huh? / 今天要不要去钓个鱼或挖个矿啊？",
        "Indoor_Day_Alex": "The sun's shining and I'm bursting with energy! You'd better watch out! Heh Heh.$h / 阳光明媚，而我也充满活力！所以你最好小心哦！嘿嘿。$h",
        "winter_Harvey": "Winter is flu season, so work is probably going to be a lot more stressful. Sorry in advance if I'm grouchy. / 冬天是流感盛行的季节，所以工作起来可能会更有压力吧。我先提前道个歉，估计之后我又要发牢骚了。",
        "Good_4": "This place is my home now... I'm happy here.$l / 以后这里就是我的家了……我在这里很幸福。$l",
        "fall_Leah": "Breathe deep... can you smell that? That tells me it's mushroom season. / 深呼吸……你闻到了吗？这气味说明蘑菇生长的季节到了。",
        "Bad_8": "You've been so cold to me lately...$s / 最近你对我好冷淡……$s",
        "spring_Sam": "*sniff* ... My doze is stubbed up... allergies. / *吸气*……鼻子都堵着了……过敏。",
        "TwoKids_1": "We have to make sure and give %kid1 a lot of attention now that we have %kid2. We don't want any jealousy between them. / 有了%kid2后，我们要记得多关注些%kid1。我不想让他们嫉妒对方。",
        "Indoor_Day_Sebastian": "Well, this place sure beats my old basement room, doesn't it?$h / 嗯，这里确实完爆我那间老旧的地下室啊，不是吗？$h",
        "Neutral_0": "I hope you'll still like me when I'm old and gray.$s / 等到我白发苍苍，我希望你还会喜爱我。$s",
        "summer_Penny": "Are you growing any melons this summer? / 今年夏天你种西瓜了吗？",
        "summer_1": "Make sure you don't get a heat stroke, dear. / 千万别中暑啊，亲爱的。#$e#Drink plenty of water and don't overwork yourself. / 要多喝水，别累着自己。",
        "Indoor_Night_Maru": "You look like you're ready for bed, @. Should I lull you to sleep with the technical details of my latest project?$h / 是准备上床了吗，@。要不要我讲些我最新项目的技术细节来催你入睡？$h#$e#*yawn*... To be honest, I'm kind of sleepy too. / *哈欠*……说实话，我也有点困了。",
        "Outdoor_Emily": "You're doing great work, @. Keep it up. / @，你做得很好。坚持下去。",
        "Rainy_Day_Abigail": "The countryside looks more interesting on a day like this, don't you think? / 郊外的景色在这种天气下应该会更有趣，你不觉得吗？",
        "Bad_3": "Did I do something wrong? You've been acting different lately.$s / 我做错什么了吗？你最近的反应不太一样。$s",
        "winter_Emily": "Whoops, my hair is frozen solid again.$s / 哎呦，我的头发又凝固了。$s",
        "Outdoor_Sebastian": "This is so different from my old life, but I'm really starting to like it.$h / 这和我以前的生活大不相同，但我真的开始爱上这里了。$h#$e#I feel like I really belong here.$l / 我觉得我真的属于这里。$l",
        "Rainy_Night_2": "Ah...The soothing sound of rain overhead... I'm going to sleep well tonight.$h / 头顶传来舒心的雨声……今晚可以睡个好觉了。$h",
        "Indoor_Night_Sam": "#$c .5#I wonder if the moon is visible tonight? / #$c .5#不知道今天能不能看到月亮呢？#$e#So, did you get everything done on the farm today? If you didn't I won't be mad! / 对了，今天所有的农活你都做完了吗？就算没有我也不会生气啦。",
        "Indoor_Day_Abigail": "There's always something new happening on our farm... I love it. / 我们的农场总是有新鲜事发生……我爱这样的生活。",
        "Rainy_Night_0": "The rain makes it feel like we're all alone.$l / 这雨让我觉得世上好像只剩我们两个人。$l#$e#I'm cold... Aren't you ready to tuck into bed?$l / 我好冷啊……你不打算钻进被窝吗？$l",
        "Indoor_Day_Penny": "This place is so big compared to the trailer, I feel overwhelmed... In a good way! / 这里比房车大多了，我有点适应不了……但这是好事！",
        "summer_Abigail": "Oh man... I could go for some chocolate cake. / 哎哟……我真想吃巧克力蛋糕。",
        "Indoor_Night_Elliott": "#$c .5#You always smell so good after a day of hard work. It's your natural musk! / #$c .5#在一天的辛勤劳作之后，你身上有种特别好闻的香味。是你的天然香味！^You smell sweet, my dear. Like a honeycomb drifting on a pool of spice tea. / 亲爱的，你身上有股甜味。就好像香料茶上漂浮的蜂蜜。#$e#Come here, let me massage your back. You look tense.$l / 来，让我给你按摩按摩背。你看起来有点紧张。$l^You smell sweet, my dear. Like a cinnamon leaf floating in the summer breeze. / 亲爱的，你身上有股甜味。就像在夏日微风中摇曳的肉桂叶。",
        "Rainy_Day_Harvey": "Make sure you stay dry today, dear. I don't want you to become hypothermic. / 亲爱的，千万别淋雨哦。我可不想让你冻着了。",
        "Indoor_Night_Leah": "It's so quiet and peaceful in the evening. Nothing to distract you from the experience of living. / 晚上真是安宁平静啊。没有东西打扰你享受生活的乐趣。",
        "summer_15": "It's summer... that means the house is full of flies. / 夏天到了……估计要满房子苍蝇了。#$e#Don't worry, I'll take care of them. / 别担心，我会处理它们的。",
        "jobLeave_Harvey": "I have to go into the clinic today. Have a nice day, okay? / 今天我得去诊所。一定要照顾好自己，好吗？",
        "fall_Harvey": "I could sure go for some wine. / 我真想喝点红酒。",
        "Good_8": "Don't worry about me... I know you've got a lot of responsibilities outside of the house. I'm fine in here by myself!$l / 别担心我……我知道你在外面担负着许多责任。我自己一个人没事的！$l",
        "fall_Shane": "I think there might be a new species of fungus growing behind my mini-fridge. / 我认为可能会有一种新的真菌生长在我的迷你冰箱里。#$e#Ah well, 'tis the season, right? / 哎，反正这季节就是这样，对吧？",
        "Rainy_Night_4": "I made some soup for dinner. [199 218 219 727 730]$h / 我晚餐做了汤。[199 218 219 727 730]$h#$e#You need something hot on a day like this!$h / 这种天气就多吃些热的东西吧！$h",
        "Neutral_2": "Taking a break? I guess being a farmer is easier than I thought... / 在休息吗？我猜当一名农夫要比我想的简单……",
        "Outdoor_Shane": "I dunno if my lungs can handle this freshness. I'm still used to JojaAir. / 我不知道如果我的肺能处理这样的新鲜。我比较习惯 Joja 空气。",
        "Outdoor_Haley": "Looks like a good day to work on my tan, don't you think, sweetheart?$h / 甜心，你不觉得今天是个晒太阳的好日子吗？$h",
        "OneKid_2": "Don't worry, I'll feed %kid1 today. You can just focus on running the farm. / 别担心，今天我来喂%kid1。你就专心经营农场吧。",
        "spring_Alex": "Hey @. Let's work hard today! / 嘿，@。今天我们都要努力工作哦！",
        "spouseRoom_Emily": "I'm going to spend some time with the parrot today. It breaks my heart that he'll never fly again.$u / 我今天将花一些时间陪伴鹦鹉。它永远也不会飞了，真令我伤心。$u",
        "Rainy_Day_3": "What's on your agenda today, dear? / 亲爱的，今天你有什么安排吗？#$e#I don't want to go outside in this weather... I'll just do some things around the house. / 这种天气我可不想出去……我就在家里忙活吧。#$e#Maybe I'll make something hot for dinner. / 要不晚餐就做点热乎的吧。",
        "Rainy_Night_1": "Make sure you change into something warm. I don't want you to get sick. / 记得穿厚点。我不希望你生病。#$e#Can you hear the rain pattering on the roof, @? / 你能听到屋顶上雨水滴滴答答的声音吗，@？",
        "fall_8": "Winter's just around the corner. We need to double check the heating system, turn off the valves, and check all the insulation in the house. / 冬天近在眼前。我们需要再次检查一下供暖系统，关掉水阀，检查房子里所有的保温层。#$e#Don't worry, I'll take care of it all. / 别担心，我会搞定一切的。",
        "Rainy_Night_3": "The rain makes our home seem so cozy.$h / 下雨天里，我们的家看起来格外温馨呢。$h^It's nights like this I'm glad we have a quality roof. / 在这样的雨夜，我好庆幸我们有个完好的屋顶。",
        "Outdoor_Abigail": "I'm just going to hang out here, okay? / 我就在这逛逛，可以吗？#$e#There's a lot of interesting bugs and things out here. *chuckle*$h / 这儿有许多有趣的虫子和小东西。*轻笑*$h",
        "winter_1": "Brrr.... It's cold. I guess winter has arrived. / 哎呀……好冷啊。我猜已经冬天了。",
        "Rainy_Day_4": "Any dinner requests for tonight? / 今晚想吃点什么？",
        "Outdoor_Maru": "I like being out here. It's a good place to think about new inventions.$h / 我喜欢呆在这外面。这是个思考新发明的好地方。$h#$e#I'm still hoping to come up with something to help you out in your work. / 我还在想能帮你分担些工作的点子。",
        "Rainy_Day_Penny": "I think I might do some baking today.$h / 我看我今天就烤些东西吃吧。$h",
        "fall_Elliott": "Ah... Fall. The warm sun drifts low in the sky, casting long shadows over waving fields of gold. / 啊……秋天。温暖的太阳低挂在天边，在金色田野的波浪上抛下长长的影子。#$e#It's a beautiful time of year, don't you think? / 真是每年最美的时刻之一，你不觉得吗？",
        "Indoor_Day_Maru": "If you ever want to talk about how to maximize crop yield or anything... I'm open to that! / 要是你想谈谈如何最大化农作物产量之类的……我随时奉陪！",
        "Rainy_Night_Harvey": "Hi. It's good to see you.$h / 嗨。很高兴见到你。$h#$e#I spent the day skimming through some medical journals. / 这一整天我都在翻阅医学期刊。",
        "jobReturn_Penny": "#$c .5#Good evening. My day was fine, thanks! How was yours?$h / #$c .5#晚上好。我今天很不错，多谢关心！你怎么样？$h#$e#Jas and Vincent weren't behaving very well today. I'm still all wound up... / 今天贾斯和文森特很不乖啊。我到现在都像上了发条一样……",
        "spouseRoom_Alex": "#$c .5#Don't ever let me get lazy. I want to stay in good shape for you! / #$c .5#不要纵容我偷懒。我要为你保持好身材。#$e#There's lots of room here to do my exercises. I'm making more progress than ever! / 这里有很大的空间供我锻炼。我现在可是进步神速！",
        "Rainy_Night_Krobus": "The sound of the rain reminds me of the sewers... it's comforting. / 雨点的声音让我想起了下水道……那里真的很舒适。#$e#The sewers were my refuge... I felt safe there. But don't worry... I feel the same way about my new home, too. / 下水道曾是我的避难所……我在那里有安全感。不过别担心……我在新家里也是同样的感受。",
        "Indoor_Night_Alex": "My arms feel a little restless... How about a nice, deep massage?$l / 我的手臂有些不舒服了……做个深层按摩怎么样？$l^I feel exhausted... That's a good sign! It means I worked hard enough today.$h / 我感到精疲力竭……这是件好事！说明我今天很努力。$h",
        "winter_Sam": "I've given up on being a musician. I'm a family man now! / 我决定不做音乐家了。我现在要当居家好男人！",
        "fall_Sebastian": "My mother used to always make this delicious pumpkin soup in the fall. / 我母亲总是会在秋天煮美味的南瓜汤。",
        "Indoor_Night_Haley": "You look like you've been working hard, dear. Let me help you de-stress.$l / 亲爱的，你看起来干了不少活啊。让我帮你减减压。$l",
        "fall_Penny": "It's so peaceful out here on the farm. I never appreciated nature that much living in town. / 农场这边真是平静啊。在城里住的时候我都没法这样欣赏自然。",
        "spring_Haley": "Aren't you glad winter's over, honey? Things seem more hopeful now. / 甜心，冬天结束了你不开心吗？现在一切又充满了希望。",
        "fall_Sam": "I wonder what's going on in the rest of the world? We're really secluded here. / 不知道外面的世界怎么样了？我们在这里真是与世隔绝啊。",
        "spring_Shane": "Maybe I'll learn a new skill this year... / 也许我今年会学习一项新技能……",
        "Good_0": "It's hard to believe we're finally married...$l / 真不敢相信我们结婚了……$l",
        "Indoor_Day_Leah": "Mind if I add some architectural flair to the woodwork around here? My chisel hand is itching! / 如果我在这儿的木制品上发挥点建筑天赋，你不会介意吧？我拿着凿子的手都发痒了！",
        "Indoor_Day_Sam": "There's too much stuff I want to get done today... Maybe I'll just watch TV instead. / 我今天想做的事情实在是太多了……也许我还是看电视好了。",
        "winter_7": "Are you going to enter the fishing contest tomorrow? / 你要参加今年的钓鱼大赛吗？",
        "NoBed_1": "I wasn't able to sleep well last night...$s / 我昨晚没睡好……$s",
        "winter_Maru": "Spring is coming soon. I'm really looking forward to having rhubarb pie. / 春天即将来临。我十分期待大黄派呢。",
        "Indoor_Night_2": "I'm glad you're home. / 很高兴你回来了。#$e#I get kind of scared alone at night.$s / 我晚上自己一个人会害怕的。$s^I get lonely at night...$s / 晚上我也总是很孤单呢……$s#$e#...$h / ……$h",
        "spouseRoom_Elliott": "#$c .5#I think I might do some writing today. / #$c .5#今天我就写点东西吧。#$e#Will you be okay without my help? / 你自己一个人干活没问题吗？",
        "Good_1": "You know, I always had a feeling we'd be together some day.$l / 你知道吗，我一直感觉我们总有一天会在一起的。$l",
        "fall_15": "Have you figured out what you're going to use for our grange display tomorrow? / 你想好了明天在农庄展览上展示什么吗？",
        "Neutral_6": "I wonder what everyone in town is doing today? / 不知道镇里的朋友们今天会做些什么呢？",
        "NoBed_3": "Did something happen to our bed...?$s / 我们的床怎么了……？$s",
        "spring_Sebastian": "Wow, my skin is pale... I guess I'd better help you with some farm work this season. / 哇，我的皮肤好苍白啊……也许这个季度我该帮你做点农活。",
        "Rainy_Day_0": "It's raining outside. Make sure you don't catch cold, dear. / 外面下雨了。亲爱的，小心别感冒哦。#$e#Stay indoors as much as possible.$h / 尽量待在屋里吧。$h#$e#I worry about you sometimes! / 有时候真是担心你啊！",
        "Outdoor_Penny": "I'm really happy on our little farm, @.$h / 我在我们的小农场里十分幸福，@。$h",
        "jobReturn_Harvey": "#$c .5#Hi, honey. How was your day? / #$c .5#嗨，甜心！今天过得怎么样？#$e#*Phew*... I'm exhausted...$s / *呼*……我要累得不行了……$s#$e#My patients are still healthy, so it was a good day. / 我的病人还很健康，所以今天还不错。",
        "spring_1": "Well, a new year has arrived. Do you have a plan for what you want to accomplish this year? / 新的一年到来了。你对今年要达成的目标有计划吗？#$e#I feel pretty hopeful. / 我觉得很有希望。",
        "Bad_0": "...Do you still love me?$s / ……你还爱我吗？$s",
        "Rainy_Day_Sebastian": "I got up just before dawn and took a walk around the farm. It's really peaceful at that hour. / 天还没亮我就起来了，然后在农场里转了会儿。黎明前的农场真是平静啊。",
        "NoBed_2": "I had to sleep on the floor last night...$s / 我昨晚只能睡在地上……$s",
        "Rainy_Day_Maru": "Despite all the technology we have, a rainy day is still the best tool for watering crops. / 虽然现在技术很发达，但雨天还是灌溉作物最好的工具。",
        "Outdoor_1": "I'm just going to relax and inspect the farm today, okay? / 我今天就放松一下，接着检视农场怎么样？#$e#It's just such a nice-looking area.$h / 这一带风景真是不错呢。$h",
        "Outdoor_Sam": "Hey, look at those puffy clouds in the sky, honey!$h / 嘿，甜心，你看天上那蓬松的云朵！$h#$e#I'm going to watch those for a while, if you don't mind. / 你不介意的话，我就在这儿多看一会儿。",
        "spouseRoom_Maru": "#$c .5#I got up early to do a little star-gazing. / #$c .5#今天我提早起来看了会儿星星。#$e#I hope you don't mind if I spend some time on my projects today, honey. / 甜心，我今天要去做我的项目，希望你不会介意。",
        "Indoor_Day_3": "Did you have any strange dreams last night? / 昨晚你有没有做奇怪的梦？#$e#I did, but all I remember is that it had something to do with a %adj %noun. Weird.$s / 我做梦了，但我只记得好像和%adj%noun有关。奇怪。$s#$e#Hehe. Dreams don't mean anything... do they, Honey?$l / 呵呵。梦境并没什么意义……是吧，甜心？$l#$e#Well, we can't spend all day chit-chatting. You have work to do! / 好了，我们可不能整天都在闲聊。你还有事要做呢！",
        "spring_Harvey": "Let's plant some healthy vegetables this spring.$h / 今年春天我们种些有益健康的蔬菜吧。$h",
        "Rainy_Night_Shane": "I just got off the phone with Jas and Marnie. They seem to be having a pretty good time without me. / 我刚挂断贾斯和玛妮的电话。没有我，他们似乎玩儿的很开心。",
        "Outdoor_Leah": "Wow, this is great! I'm really starting to enjoy life on the farm, @.$h / 哇，太棒了！我开始喜欢上农场的生活了，@。$h#$e#This is the life I've always dreamed of.$l / 这简直就是我梦寐以求的生活啊。$l",
        "winter_Abigail": "Remember when we played that 'Prairie King' game together, in my room? Those were good times.$h / 还记得以前我们一起在我屋里玩“草原之王”的游戏吗？那时真是开心。$h",
        "Outdoor_Elliott": "Today, I'm going to continue writing my new novel. What better place than our wonderful farm?$h / 今天，我要继续写我的新小说。还有比我们的农场更好的地方吗？$h#$e#This is perfect.$l / 这里简直完美。$l",
        "Neutral_1": "Do you think your grandpa would be proud of the work we've done? / 你觉得爷爷会为我们做的事感到骄傲吗？",
        "winter_Leah": "I always start craving salad in the winter... Inconvenient, I know. / 冬天我总是想吃蔬菜沙拉……我也知道这不太方便。",
        "Outdoor_2": "Hi, honey! If I knew more about farm work I'd help you out more. Sorry! / 嗨，甜心！要是我多懂些耕种的知识，我一定会多帮帮你的。对不起！#$e#I'll be thinking of you.$h / 我会一直想着你的。$h",
        "summer_Haley": "You must know by now that summer is my favorite season.$h / 你现在一定猜到了，我最喜欢的季节就是夏天。$h",
        "summer_Harvey": "Make sure you don't get sunburnt, honey... That can really damage your skin. / 千万别晒伤了，甜心……那对你皮肤不好。",
        "spouseRoom_Leah": "#$c .5#One of these days I'll have to do your portrait. / #$c .5#等有一天，我要给你画幅肖像画。#$e#The view from this window is inspiring, don't you think? / 你不觉得窗外的景色充满了灵感吗？",
        "OneKid_1": "I wonder if %kid1 will grow up to be a farmer like you? / 不知道%kid1将来会不会像你一样成为农夫呢？",
        "Neutral_9": "I wonder if we'll live here our entire lives? / 不知道我们这辈子会不会一直住在这里？",
        "Indoor_Night_0": "Did you get everything done today, @? / 今天的事都做完了吗，@？#$e#I did some house chores... but now I'm so tired. / 我做了些家务……但现在好累啊。#$e#I'm ready for bed whenever you are.$h / 你准备好了我们就上床睡觉吧。$h",
        "spring_Leah": "Don't forget to look for wild horseradish, leeks and dandelions while you're out there! / 出去的时候，别忘了找找野山葵、韭菜和蒲公英！",
        "winter_Elliott": "I think I might do some writing this winter. There's not much else to do, anyway. / 今年冬天我准备写点东西。反正也没多少事可做。",
        "spring_Penny": "I'm so happy to see some greenery after that long white winter. / 白茫茫的冬季过后，绿葱葱的景象真是让人欣喜。",
        "TwoKids_0": "I already gave %kid1 and %kid2 their breakfast. They were hungry! / 我已经给%kid1和%kid2做过早餐了。他们是真饿了！",
        "Indoor_Day_Harvey": "The sky looks great today... so clear! / 今天的天空太美了……如此澄澈！#$e#From now on, I'm only going to go into the clinic when I have appointments. Otherwise I can just work from home! / 从现在起，我打算只有接到预约才去诊所。平时我就在家办公吧！",
        "Rainy_Night_Elliott": "Sit down, relax! You've got to be tired after trudging through the mud all day. / 快坐下，放轻松！白天在泥地里干了一天活，你一定累了吧。",
        "Bad_6": "We only have one short life to live... is this the best way to do it?$s / 我们的人生短暂……就这样子度过真的好吗？$s",
        "spouseRoom_Abigail": "#$c .5#I got up a little before you and fed David Jr. He's very active this morning. / #$c .5#我提前起床给小大卫喂了吃的。今早他很有活力。#$e#I hope you don't mind the guinea pig smell. / 我希望你不会介意豚鼠的味道。",
        "Indoor_Night_1": "Wow, you look like you did a lot of work today. / 哇，你今天好像干了不少活啊。#$e#Now you should just relax and kick back for the night.$h / 现在，你就放轻松，好好休息一晚吧。$h",
        "Rainy_Night_Abigail": "I'm ready to hop into bed whenever you are. The sound of rain will put us right to sleep. / 如果你准备睡了，我随时可以上床陪你。听着雨声很快就能入睡了。",
        "Outdoor_Harvey": "This is so much nicer than being cooped up in the clinic all day.$l / 这要比整天窝在诊所里好多了。$l#$e#I love watching you on the farm... hehe / 我还爱看你耕种的样子……呵呵。",
        "fall_1": "This weather feels pretty nice after the heat of summer. / 炎夏过后，这天气真是令人舒爽。",
        "jobLeave_Penny": "I have to go into town today. Don't work too hard, and eat something good for lunch!$h / 我今天要去镇里一趟。别太辛苦了，午饭吃点好的！$h",
        "Good_5": "I was just admiring my wedding amulet... The shell is flawless. It must have cost you a fortune!$l / 我刚刚在欣赏我的婚礼护身符呢……这贝壳完美无瑕。一定花了你很多钱吧。$l",
        "Rainy_Night_Alex": "Grandma always used to make hot stew on nights like this.$h / 在这样的晚上，奶奶总会炖上一锅热汤。$h",
        "Rainy_Day_Krobus": "Ah, it's more humid today with the rain... I feel a lot more comfortable. / 啊，今天下了雨，空气更潮湿了……我感觉更加舒服了。",
        "spouseRoom_Harvey": "#$c .5#No air-traffic this morning, honey. But it's still fun to break out the equipment now and then. / #$c .5#甜心，今早没什么飞机来啊。但偶尔调试一下设备也很有趣。#$e#I'm working on a new model plane. It's so much more relaxing here than in my old apartment. / 我正在制作新的飞机模型。在这要比在我那破旧的公寓轻松多了。",
        "Indoor_Day_2": "Did you sleep well? / 睡得还好吗？#$e#I've got some chores to do in here. / 我还要做些家务。",
        "Neutral_5": "Are we doing okay on money, @? / 家里是不是有些拮据，@？",
        "Indoor_Night_4": "*phew*! I just finished my chores. Now we can spend some time together.$h / *呼*！我刚做完家务。现在我们可以共处一段时间了。$h#$e#So, tell me about your day.$l / 给我讲讲你今天怎么过的吧。$l#$e#...$h / ……$h",
        "spouseRoom_Penny": "#$c .5#I always wanted my very own library. This is so charming.$h / #$c .5#我一直想拥有自己的图书馆。这真是太好了。$h#$e#I like to do a little reading first thing in the morning. It gets my brain into gear. / 早上我准备先读点东西。让我的脑袋开动起来。",
        "summer_Emily": "Phew! It's hot but it feels great, doesn't it? / 咻！很热，但感觉很好，不是吗？#$e#Maybe we'll see some wild parrots today. / 也许今天我们会看到一些野生鹦鹉。",
        "spring_Elliott": "I'm looking forward to a beautiful year on %farm farm.$h / 希望今年%farm农场能风调雨顺，一切都好。$h",
        "fall_26": "Should we go to the Spirit's Eve festival tomorrow night? / 明晚我们是不是该去万灵节？",
        "summer_Elliott": "One of the main things I miss about the ocean is the fresh fish. / 说起大海，我最想念的是那里新鲜的鱼。",
        "Rainy_Day_Elliott": "The rain makes me think of my old life by the ocean. / 雨天又让我回想起以前在海边的日子了。#$e#Change is part of life. That's okay. / 没关系，改变也是生活的一部分。",
        "summer_8": "Sorry if I smell... I was sweating all night in the heat. / 抱歉我身上有异味……今晚热得我全身冒汗。",
        "Good_3": "Wow, you look really handsome today!$l / 哇哦，你今天看起来帅呆了！$l^Wow, you look beautiful today.$l / 哇哦，你今天看起来美极了。$l",
        "Outdoor_Alex": "I'm going to get a bunch of exercise today! Haha! I love living on a farm.$h / 我今天要做很多运动！哈哈！我爱农场的生活。$h",
        "Bad_7": "I used to be your sweetie... now you only seem to put up with me when I make a hot dinner.$s / 我曾经是你眼中的宝贝……但现在，只有做顿热腾腾的晚餐才能让你容忍我。$s",
        "Rainy_Day_2": "Good morning! I woke up early from the sound of the rain and made you some breakfast. [194 195 210 211 216]   / 早啊！我一早就被雨声弄醒了，我还给你做了些早饭。[194 195 210 211 216]#$e#Stay warm and don't work too hard. I want you to stay healthy. / 别冻着了，也不用工作那么辛苦。我希望你健健康康的。",
        "Rainy_Night_Sam": "Vincent called. He said he misses me and also to tell you hi.$h / 文森特打来电话。他说他想我了，还向你问好。$h",
        "winter_Penny": "I'm going to do a lot of reading this winter. / 今年冬天我准备多读读书。",
        "Outdoor_4": "Don't overwork yourself, dear. / 亲爱的，别累着自己了。#$e#Make sure and take a break every now and then, or get something to eat.$h / 记得不时地休息一下，或者吃点东西。$h",
        "spouseRoom_Sebastian": "#$c .5#I'm debating whether I should work or just read comics all day. / #$c .5#我在想我今天是工作还是看一整天漫画。#$e#Hey, do we have any pizza in the freezer? I'm hungry. / 嘿，我们冰箱里有披萨吗？我饿了。",
        "OneKid_0": "Have you spent any time with %kid1 today? / 你今天有花时间陪%kid1玩耍吗？",
        "Indoor_Day_Krobus": "I wish I could help you on the farm, but I can't go out in the sun... / 我很希望能到农场上帮你，但是我没法呆在太阳底下……",
        "summer_Maru": "It's a good time of year to do some stargazing. / 每年这个时候都很适合看星星。",
        "Rainy_Night_Sebastian": "I'll never grow tired of the rain... especially out here in the countryside. / 我永远不会厌倦下雨……尤其是乡下的雨。",
        "Neutral_8": "No matter how much I clean, the house keeps getting dirty again. / 不管我怎么打扫，房子还是会变脏。#$e#I guess farms can be kind of dirty. / 也许是农场本来就挺脏的吧。",
        "jobLeave_Maru": "I have to leave for work soon. I'll see you tonight. I'll be thinking of you!$h / 我马上要去上班了。晚上见。我会一直想着你的！$h",
        "summer_Leah": "Nothing pairs so well with summer like a nice sweet wine. Don't you think, honey? / 一杯甘美的红酒配这盛夏再合适不过了。不是吗，甜心？",
        "jobReturn_Maru": "#$c .5#Well, it was just another boring day at the clinic. / #$c .5#唉，又在诊所度过了无趣的一天。#$e#Hey. Did you have a more exciting day than me? I hope so. / 嘿。你今天是不是过得比我开心？希望如此。#$e#$c .5#Well, it's time to kick back and relax. Did you leave me any dinner? / $c .5#好啦，是时候停下来休息一下了。你给我留晚饭了吗？#$e#I'm just looking forward to bed-time.$h / 我只是在期待睡觉时间。$h",
        "winter_Shane": "There's a wide, wide world out there... but I'd rather stay in my room. / 外面有一个很大很大的世界……但我宁愿呆在自己的房间里。",
        "Indoor_Day_Emily": "By providing fresh, healthy produce to the community, we're doing a great service! / 我们通过生产新鲜、健康的食物来为社区做贡献！",
        "TwoKids_3": "A nice house, two wonderful kids, and a beautiful plot of land. What's left? / 一栋漂亮的房子，两个可爱的孩子还有一方美丽的土地。夫复何求呢？",
        "Outdoor_0": "It's a beautiful day today, isn't it?$h / 今天天气不错，对吧？$h#$e#Days like this make work a little more pleasant. / 这种天气会让工作更惬意。",
        "winter_28": "Thanks for a great year, @. I'm excited to tackle next year together.$l / 感谢这美好的一年，@。我很期待与你共度明年。$l",
        "winter_Sebastian": "I wonder what Sam's up to? We used to be really good friends. / 不知道山姆怎么样了？我们以前是很要好的朋友。",
        "Indoor_Night_Penny": "Hi there, honey. Ready to spend a quiet evening at home? / 嗨，甜心。准备好在家度过平静的夜晚了吗？",
        "Rainy_Day_Emily": "I know you pride yourself on your work, but don't overdo it today. Okay, honey?$u / 我知道你为自己的工作感到自豪，但不要太过。好吧，亲爱的？$u",
        "Rainy_Day_Haley": "Hmmph. If this weather keeps up I'll get too pale.$s / 哼~~~这天气再这么下去，皮肤都要变成惨白色了。$s",
        "Rainy_Night_5": "I'm glad you're home... It's a good night to stay inside. / 你在家就好……今晚很适合待在家里。",
        "NoBed_0": "Where am I supposed to sleep...?$s / 我该睡在哪……？$s",
        "winter_Alex": "I hope my grandparents are doing okay. They used to rely on my help quite a bit. You know, with lifting heavy objects or whatever. / 希望我的祖父母一切都好。他们以前需要我帮很多忙。像是搬重物之类的。",
        "Indoor_Day_Elliott": "I've been keeping a journal ever since we moved in together. Now that I actually have a life, I have lots to write about.$h / 我们搬到这里后，我就一直坚持写日志。现在我有了自己的生活，要写的东西好多啊。$h#$e#I want to make sure I always remember these years. / 我一定要铭记在这里的日子。",
        "Bad_4": "Do you ever wonder what else is out there?$s / 你有没有想过外面还有什么新事物？$s",
        "summer_Shane": "What's on my agenda today... hmmm...  / 我今天的日程是什么……唔……#$e#I think I see some spicy pretzel snacks and a couple of 'cold boys' on the horizon. / 我想该来点辣脆饼零食和两个“冷酷男孩”雪糕。",
        "Indoor_Day_Shane": "There's something special in the air... *sniff*... what is that? Oh... / 空气中有种特别的味道……*吸气*……是什么？哦……#$b#It's just this old corn chip I put in my pocket a few weeks ago. *crunch* / ？是我几周前放在口袋里的玉米片。 *嚼嚼*",
        "Bad_5": "You used to be romantic... what happened?$s / 你以前那么浪漫……到底怎么了？$s#$e#I know I'm not as young as I used to be... is that what you married me for?$a / 我知道自己没有以前那么年轻了……难道你和我结婚就是为了我当时的年轻貌美？$a",
        "Indoor_Day_Haley": "I always feel happy on a sunny day.$h / 晴天总是让我心情舒畅。$h",
        "Rainy_Night_Maru": "Were you able to accomplish much today, hun? / 这种天气有很多事可做呢，是吧？#$e#I tried to fix up some things around the house... you know, just little stuff. / 我把房子周围修了修……一些小修补而已。",
        "Indoor_Night_3": "Are you done with your work for the day? I'm ready to have some fun.$h / 今天的事都做完了吗？我刚准备好找点乐子呢。$h#$e#But if you're tired I understand. / 不过如果你累了，我也可以理解。",
        "fall_Alex": "I feel weak... I need some protein.$s / 我觉得很虚弱……得多吃点蛋白质。$s",
        "fall_Abigail": "I hope we're growing pumpkins this year.$h / 希望今年我们会种些南瓜。$h",
        "Rainy_Night_Leah": "How was your day today, dear? Muddy? / 亲爱的，今天过得怎么样？身上没粘上泥吧？",
        "Indoor_Night_Krobus": "Hi, @. Welcome home. You look like you've been working hard out there!$h / 嗨，@。欢迎回家。看起来你干活挺辛苦的！$h",
        "Outdoor_3": "I'm just going to do some dusting over here. That should help you out, right? / 我就在这扫扫灰。这会帮到你吧？#$e#*phew*... it's hot out here. / *呼*……这儿还真热啊。",
        "spring_Abigail": "I may like the colder seasons, but by the end I'm always glad to see spring arrive. / 虽然我也喜欢冷点的季节，但最终我还是很喜欢看到春天的来临。",
        "Rainy_Day_Shane": "The roof's leaking? Ah well... a little mold never hurt anyone. / 屋顶漏水？唔……一点霉菌也无关紧要。",
        "summer_Alex": "I always have the most energy in the summer. / 在夏天，我最有活力。",
        "Good_6": "Be careful out there! Sometimes I worry about you falling into a mine shaft. / 出去要小心啊！有时我总会担心你跌到矿井里。",
        "Indoor_Day_4": "Good morning, dear. Another day of farm chores, huh? / 亲爱的，早上好。一天农活又开始了，嗯？#$e#I'll be cheering for you. <$h / 我会为你加油的。<$h",
        "summer_Sebastian": "I'm going to stay inside as much as possible this summer. / 今年夏天我就尽量待在室内吧。",
        "spouseRoom_Haley": "#$c .5#Go ahead and start your day, honey. I'm just putting on my make-up. / #$c .5#甜心，你先去忙吧。我要化个妆。#$e#Have any plans for the day? / 今天有什么打算？",
        "fall_Emily": "I drank a super-food smoothie this morning and I feel aaah-mazing!$h / 今天早上我喝了营养奶昔，感觉超超超——超棒的！$h",
        "Neutral_7": "I don't really feel like doing anything today. / 今天我真的什么都不想做。",
        "spouseRoom_Shane": "#$c .5#Beer or cider? Sometimes life can be challenging. / #$c .5#啤酒还是苹果酒？生活有时候是很有挑战性的。#$e#Hi, @. I'll just hang out in here today and uh... maybe sweep the floor a little bit or something. / 嗨，@。今天我就在这里闲逛，嗯……也许扫扫地或干点什么。",
        "Bad_1": "*sigh*... Maybe we got married too young.$s / *唉* ……也许我们结婚太早了。$s",
        "Rainy_Day_Alex": "Hmm... I guess I'll have to do push-ups and sit-ups indoors today. / 嗯……看来我今天只能在室内做俯卧撑和仰卧起坐了。",
        "Neutral_3": "If you go into town, make sure and say hi to everyone for me. / 要是你去镇子里，记得替我向大家打个招呼。",
        "Good_2": "Are you enjoying the married life, @? / 结婚了开心吗，@？#$e#I am.$l / 我准备好了。$l",
        "summer_Sam": "Summer always makes me want to eat more barbecue. / 到了夏天，我总是想多吃点烧烤。",
        "Rainy_Night_Emily": "Certain spirits only appear in the rain. Maybe you've heard their cries? / 有些幽灵只出现在雨天。你是不是已经听到他们的哭声了？",
        "Indoor_Night_Harvey": "You look like you could use a good massage tonight.$l / 看上去你今晚需要点按摩。$l#$e#Doctor's orders... It's good for the circulation! / 谨遵医嘱……这对血液循环有好处！",
        "fall_Maru": "I'm glad I still work at the clinic... It's an important service for the community. / 我很高兴仍在诊所工作……医疗服务对社区来说极为重要。",
        "Outdoor_Krobus": "On a day like this, I can enjoy the outdoors with you. This is really nice!$h / 只要是这样的天气，我就可以和你一起享受户外生活。这可真棒！$h#$b#Just let me know if you see anyone coming, so I can hide.$u / 只要你看到有人来就告诉我，这样我就可以躲起来了。$u",
        "Bad_9": "I wonder if I could've done better.$s / 也许我应该更努力些。$s",
        "Indoor_Night_Sebastian": "#$c .5#I may be a reclusive guy, but I'm always happy when you're around.$h / #$c .5#我可能是个与世隔绝的人，但你在我的身旁我就会很幸福。$h#$e#Hi, @. Good to see you. It's comforting when you're around.$h / 嗨，@。真高兴看到你。有你在我就安心了。$h",
        "spring_23": "I hope you've been practicing your moves... tomorrow is the flower dance! / 我希望你已经练过舞步了……明天是花舞节！",
        "Indoor_Night_Emily": "It's a very cozy house... I like it. / 这是一个非常舒适的房子……我喜欢它。",
        "spouseRoom_Sam": "#$c .5#The old guitar... I don't have as much drive to play it anymore. That's fine. / #$c .5#那把旧吉他……我已经失去弹奏它的动力了。不过没关系。#$e#What's on your agenda today? / 今天你怎么安排的？",
        "Indoor_Night_Shane": "How was your day? Mine actually went pretty well. / 今天过得怎么样？实际上我过得相当好。",
        "Indoor_Day_1": "Hi, honey! Smells good, doesn't it? I made you breakfast! [194 195 210 211 216] / 嗨，甜心！闻到香味了吧？我给你做了早餐！[194 195 210 211 216]#$e#You need food to stay energized throughout the day. / 要吃好吃饱，才能一天精力充沛。",
        "Indoor_Day_0": "Good morning ~<$h / 早上好 ~<$h#$e#Ready for a hard day's work? I am.$h / 今天准备好迎接忙碌的一天了吗？我准备好了。$h",
        "TwoKids_2": "You know, I think %kid2 has your nose. / 你知道吗，我觉得%kid2的鼻子像你。",
        "Rainy_Day_Sam": "I might spend some time today fixing any leaks in the roof or the windows. / 今天我可能得花时间修补一下屋顶的漏洞和窗户。",
        "Rainy_Night_Haley": "Hi, honey. I'm so glad you're home. I was starting to get kind of lonely.$l / 嗨，甜心！真高兴你回来了。我都有点孤单了。$l",
        "Indoor_Night_Abigail": "Are you ready for bed soon? I turned on the electric blanket for us...$l / 准备过一会儿就睡吗？我去把电热毯打开……$l",
        "Rainy_Day_1": "It's raining! That means we don't have to water the crops today.$h / 下雨了！所以今天我们就不用灌溉了呢。$h#$e#Nature can be a big help sometimes. / 大自然有时候也能帮大忙呢。#$e#Have you fed the animals yet, honey? / 亲爱的，你喂动物了吗？",
        "winter_Haley": "I was just thinking about the time you helped me open a jar of pickles.$h / 我又回想起你帮我开咸菜罐头的那一天。$h#$e#We've come a long way since then.$l / 我们也是在那之后好上的。$l",
        "Good_7": "@? I just want to say that I appreciate all the hard work you do for our household.$h / @？我只是想说，我要感谢你为我们一家做出的全部努力。$h",
        "OneKid_3": "Life's a lot different now that we have a child. / 自从我们有了孩子后，生活就大不相同了。",
        "Neutral_4": "I'll do the laundry tomorrow morning before you get up... that way you won't have any down-time. / 明早你起来之前我会把衣服洗了……这样你就可以专心劳作了。",
        "spring_Maru": "I'm feeling excited for a new year of farming, @!$h / 新的一年耕种开始了，我好兴奋啊，@！$h",
        "Rainy_Night_Penny": "Oh... the smell? I tried to do some baking... It didn't work out too well.$s / 啊……这个味道？我想烤些东西吃……进展不太顺利啊。$s",
        "fall_Haley": "I'm craving cake. / 好想吃蛋糕。#$e#But not just any cake... it has to be pink. / 但普通的不行……必须是粉红色的。"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/MarriageDialogueAbigail",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "spouseRoom_Abigail": "#$c .5#I got up a little before you and fed David Jr. He's very active this morning. / #$c .5#我提前起床给小大卫喂了吃的。今早他很有活力。#$e#I hope you don't mind the guinea pig smell. / 我希望你不会介意豚鼠的味道。",
        "Indoor_Night_1": "Hey! Tell me about your day. Did anything exciting happen?$h / 嘿！说说今天过得怎么样啊。发生什么令人兴奋的事了吗？$h",
        "Rainy_Night_Abigail": "The sound of rain should put us right to sleep tonight. / 听着雨声很快就能入睡了。",
        "fall_1": "The scent is unmistakable... mushroom, rotting leaves, pumpkin. It's fall, alright. Isn't it lovely? / 这香味很明显……蘑菇、腐烂的树叶、南瓜。秋天到了。很美好不是吗？",
        "Good_4": "I'm glad I owned a heavy pair of boots before moving in. It's hard to imagine tip-toeing around the mud in sneakers.$h / 幸好我在搬进来之前就有一双结实的靴子。很难想象穿着运动鞋踮着脚从泥中走过。$h",
        "Bad_8": "You've been so cold to me lately... What's wrong with you? You're acting like a bog spirit...$s / 最近你对我好冷淡……你到底是怎么回事？你简直像个泥沼精灵……$s",
        "Neutral_0": "I hope you'll still like me when I'm old and shriveled. It's going to happen some day! / 等到我白发苍苍，我希望你还会喜欢我。总会有这一天的！",
        "Good_5": "I was just admiring the mermaid's pendant you gave me... I'll proudly wear this to my grave.$l / 我只是在欣赏你送我的美人鱼吊坠……我会一直戴着它，直到生命的尽头。$l",
        "summer_1": "I get sunburnt very easily, so I need to be careful this time of year. / 我很容易晒伤，所以在每年这个时候我都需要注意。#$e#I hope you like me pale!$h / 希望你喜欢我变白的样子。$h",
        "Indoor_Day_2": "Heading to the mines? Hey... if you find something tasty, remember to bring me a piece!$h / 去矿场吗？嘿……如果你找到什么好吃的东西，记得给我带一份！$h",
        "Rainy_Day_Abigail": "The countryside looks more interesting on a day like this, don't you think? / 郊外的景色在这种天气下应该会更有趣，你不觉得吗？",
        "Indoor_Night_4": "The sounds of the night are louder out here. I'll never stop enjoying that. / 这里晚上的声音有点大。我会一直很享受它的。",
        "Rainy_Night_2": "Can you feel it? There's a stillness in the rain... / 你能感受到吗？雨的宁静……",
        "Indoor_Day_Abigail": "There's always something new happening on our farm... I love it. / 我们的农场总是有新鲜事发生……我爱这样的生活。",
        "Rainy_Night_0": "I was just gazing out into the rainswept woods... I swear I saw something darker than black shifting around the trees.$6 / 我只是在看被雨淋湿的木头……我发誓我看到什么黑漆漆的东西在树周围移动。$6",
        "summer_4": "Make sure you don't get a heat stroke, my love. / 千万别中暑啊，亲爱的。#$e#Drink plenty of water and don't overwork yourself. / 要多喝水，别累着自己。",
        "summer_Abigail": "Oh man... I could go for some chocolate cake. / 哎哟……我真想吃巧克力蛋糕。",
        "summer_15": "It's summer... that means the house is full of flies. / 夏天到了……估计要满房子苍蝇了。#$e#Don't worry, I'll take care of them. It's fun!$h / 别担心，我会处理它们的。这很好玩！$h",
        "summer_8": "Sorry about the smell... I was sweating all night in the heat. / 我对这味道感到抱歉……今晚热得我全身冒汗。",
        "Good_3": "I can't even remember the last time I dyed my hair... I swear, it never fades from this color... / 我甚至不记得上次染发是什么时候了……我发誓，我头发绝对没有褪色……",
        "Bad_7": "I used to be special to you, your best friend... now you only seem to put up with me when I make a hot dinner.$s / 我曾经对你来说很特别……但现在，只有做顿热腾腾的晚餐才能让你容忍我。$s",
        "Rainy_Night_4": "I felt like making some soup for dinner. I hope it's not too disgusting. [199 218 219 727 730]$h / 我晚餐想做汤。希望不要太难喝……[199 218 219 727 730]$h",
        "fall_20": "Honey... you're worth more to me than a chest full of quartz. / 亲爱的……你对我来说比满箱的水晶更珍贵。#$e#Now, a chest full of amethyst? Hmm... I'd have to think about that one.$h / 那，一箱紫水晶呢？嗯……这个我得想想。$h",
        "Rainy_Day_2": "Hey! I woke up early and did some exploring on my own. I found this and it reminded me of you. [768 767 769 66 82] / 嘿！我今天早起并自己去探险了。我发现了这个，这让我想到了你。[768 767 769 66 82]#$e#Think you can find something better than that? I'm not so sure!$h / 你觉得自己能找到比这更好的吗？我可不敢肯定！$h",
        "funLeave_Abigail": "I'm going in to town today, just so you know. I need to stretch these legs a bit. / 告诉你一声，我今天要去小镇。我得去活动一下筋骨。",
        "Outdoor_4": "I always forget to put some snacks in my pocket. *rumble*$h / 我总是忘记在口袋里面放一些零食。*肚子咕咕叫*$h",
        "Neutral_8": "No matter how much we clean, the house keeps getting dirty again. / 不管我们怎么打扫，房子还是会变脏。#$e#I guess farms are kind of dirty. / 也许是农场本来就挺脏的吧。",
        "Rainy_Day_3": "It might be a good day to visit the caves, huh? Just be careful out there. / 今天可能很适合去山洞，对吧？不过要小心啊。#$e#If you go, bring a Life Elixir or two. / 如果你要去的话，记得带上几瓶生命药水。",
        "Rainy_Night_1": "It's a good night to see a ghost... / 今晚很适合看鬼魂……",
        "fall_6": "Ah... fall. This might be my favorite time of year. The colors really complement my hair, don't you think? / 啊……秋天啊。这可能是一年里面我最喜欢的时光。秋天的颜色真的很配我的头发，你觉得呢？",
        "TwoKids_3": "A cool old house, a couple kids, and an amazing farm. I never thought I'd come this far... but, hey! Our lives are just getting started.$h / 一间酷酷的老房子，几个孩子，还有美好的农场。从没料到我会过上今天这样的生活……不过呢！我们的生活才刚刚开始。$h",
        "Outdoor_0": "The soft breeze is blowing mountain air throughout the valley today. It smells like fresh pine and sage. / 今天谷里吹过微风，抚动山里的空气。闻起来像清新的松树和洋苏草。",
        "Rainy_Night_3": "On nights like this, I like to turn the light down low and just listen...$8 / 在这样的夜晚里，我喜欢把灯调暗，静静聆听……$8",
        "Outdoor_Abigail": "I'm just going to hang out here, okay? / 我就在这逛逛，可以吗？#$e#There's a lot of interesting bugs and things out here. *chuckle*$h / 这儿有许多有趣的虫子和小东西。*轻笑*$h",
        "Rainy_Day_4": "Maybe I'll boot up Journey Of The Prairie King today... one of these days I swear, I'll beat the whole game.$h / 或许今天我会玩“草原之王的冒险之旅”……我发誓总有一天我能自己通关。$h",
        "fall_2": "Can we grow giant pumpkins this season? Please, honey?$h / 这个季节我们可以种巨型南瓜吗？亲爱的？$h",
        "Rainy_Night_5": "Hey! You look like you've been hard at work. Can I help you relax? / 嘿！你看起来干活儿很卖力啊。我能帮你放松吗？^Have you been working hard? You look cute when you're a little exhausted.$h / 你干活儿一直很卖力吗？你精疲力尽的样子真可爱。$h",
        "Indoor_Night_3": "*yawn*... I'm ready to call it a night pretty soon.$h / *哈欠*……我马上就准备好收工睡觉了。$h",
        "fall_Abigail": "Do I smell pumpkin on you? Maybe I'm just dreaming...$h / 我是在你身上闻到南瓜的味道了吗？可能我是在做梦吧……$h",
        "winter_3": "I actually like the cold weather. It just gives me an excuse to get cozy!$h / 实际上我喜欢冷天。给了我一个安逸的理由！$h",
        "Outdoor_3": "It's pretty cool that we have a cave on our property. It's something I always dreamed about.$h / 我们拥有一个山洞，这太酷了！简直让我梦想成真了。$h",
        "spring_Abigail": "I may like the colder seasons, but by the end I'm always glad to see spring arrive. / 虽然我也喜欢冷点的季节，但最终我还是很喜欢看到春天的来临。",
        "patio_Abigail": "%Abigail is lost in her music. / %阿比盖尔正沉醉在她的音乐里。",
        "Indoor_Day_4": "You don't mind if I do some re-decorating now and then, do you? I'm still excited to have a place of my own to work on. / 我偶尔重新装修一下你是不会介意的，对吧？有片能自己装修的地方仍让我感到兴奋。",
        "Good_6": "Hey. I know you're smart, but I still worry about you sometimes. The world is full of monsters.$6 / 嘿。我知道你很聪明，但有时候我还是会担心你。这世界上到处都是怪物。$6#$e#Just promise me you'll be careful. I don't want to lose you. / 答应我你会小心。我不想失去你。",
        "winter_15": "It's fun to explore the valley in winter! Everything is so different under a blanket of snow. And so quiet... / 冬天去谷里探险很有趣！在一层大雪的掩盖下，一切都大不相同。并且很安静……",
        "Neutral_7": "If you moved on to the spirit world, I'd set up a little shrine for you next to Grandpa's. / 如果你去了灵界，我会在爷爷旁边为你设一个小神龛。",
        "Indoor_Night_2": "I used to be a night owl, but I'm starting to enjoy the rhythm of life on the farm. It feels natural. / 我曾经是个夜猫子，但是我正开始享受农场生活的节奏。感觉很自然。",
        "Good_1": "Did you hear that? Sometimes I'm convinced this house is haunted.$u / 你听到那声音了吗？有时候我觉得这栋房子闹鬼。$u",
        "Neutral_6": "I wonder how the old shop is doing? I should visit my parents again soon. / 不知道老店怎么样了？我应该尽早再去探望一下父母。",
        "Good_2": "Welwick's horoscope predicted great things for me today. I feel really motivated! / 维尔维克占星预言说我今天会发生大好事。我感觉充满了干劲！",
        "Rainy_Day_0": "The dark... the rain... it gets me excited.$l / 这夜色……这雨……让我很兴奋。$l",
        "spring_1": "So, do you have any big plans for the new year? / 话说，你对新的一年有什么大计划吗？",
        "Bad_9": "I wonder if I could've done better... I was very good friends with Sebastian before we met. He was probably the one...$s / 不知道我是不是选错了……在我们相遇之前我和塞巴斯蒂安就是好朋友。也许他才是那个唯一……$s",
        "Outdoor_1": "Hmm... I think we've got plenty of space for outdoor slime ranching! / 嗯……我想我们已经有很大的空间来放养史莱姆了！",
        "Indoor_Day_3": "Hey! I'm just debating what I should do today. I'm not used to having this much freedom! / 嘿！我只是在想我今天应该干嘛。我还不习惯这么自由！",
        "spring_2": "Do you have any new year's resolutions? I'm trying to lose a few pounds around the middle.$h / 新年你有什么目标吗？我正努力在半年内减轻一些体重。$h",
        "Indoor_Day_1": "Hey, @. Heading out into the wild? I got you something...[286 287 205 732] / 嘿，@。去野外吗？我有东西要给你……[286 287 205 732]#$e#Use that if you get into a tough spot. It should help keep you safe. / 在你处境艰难的时候可以用得上。这应该能确保你的安全。",
        "winter_Abigail": "Remember when we played 'Prairie King' together in my room, so long ago? Those were good times.$h / 还记得很久以前我们一起在我屋里玩“草原之王”的游戏吗？那时真是开心。$h",
        "Indoor_Day_0": "I always loved this place, long before you moved in. Now I can explore the farm whenever I want!$h / 在你搬进来之前我就一直很喜欢这个地方。现在我随时都能探索农场了！$h",
        "TwoKids_2": "I had a dream that %kid2 will grow up to be a famous monster hunter. I've already been thinking about a little armor set. / 我梦到%kid2将成为一名著名的怪物猎人。我已经在考虑做一套小装备了。",
        "Indoor_Night_Abigail": "Are you ready for bed soon? I turned on the electric blanket for us...$l / 准备过一会儿就睡吗？我去把电热毯打开……$l",
        "Neutral_1": "Do you think your Grandpa would be proud of us? / 你觉得爷爷会为我们感到骄傲吗？",
        "Rainy_Day_1": "Hey, remember when we played that duet by the lake? This weather reminds me of that day. / 嘿，还记得我们之前在湖边对唱吗？这天气让我想起了那天。#$e#You really surprised me with that mini-harp... I never expected that. I guess that's why I like you so much.$l / 你用那迷你竖琴惊艳到我了……完全出乎我的意料。我猜这就是我这么喜欢你的原因。$l",
        "Outdoor_2": "Make sure to keep things tidy around your Grandpa's shrine. There's something special about it, I can feel it. / 保持你爷爷神龛干净整洁。我能感觉到，它有些特殊之处。",
        "Good_7": "@? I just want to say that I appreciate all the hard work you do for us. I'm really proud of you.$l / @？我只是想说，我要感谢你为我们做出的一切努力。我真为你感到骄傲。$l",
        "OneKid_3": "I can't believe I'm a \"mom\"... life is weird.$h / 我真不敢相信我是一位“妈妈”了……生活真奇妙。$h",
        "spring_12": "Hey, the egg festival is tomorrow. I'm sorry, but I won't go easy on you because we're married!$h / 嘿，明天就是复活节了。抱歉，但我不会因为我们结婚了而手下留情的！$h#$e#I plan on winning that egg hunt. Go ahead and try to beat me. / 我要成为彩蛋大寻宝的赢家。你尽管试着打败我吧。",
        "Neutral_9": "I wonder if we'll live here our entire lives? I might get bored. / 不知道我们会不会这辈子一直住在这里？我可能会觉得无聊。",
        "Indoor_Night_0": "I had a good day, today. There's always something interesting going on around here, if you look close enough. / 今天我过得很愉快。如果你留心观察的话，就会发现这里总在发生些有趣的事儿。",
        "funReturn_Abigail": "Hey! Did you have a good day? Mine went well. It was refreshing to take a walk.$h / 嘿！你过得好吗？我过得挺好。散散步让人精神清爽。$h",
        "TwoKids_0": "I already gave %kid1 and %kid2 their chocolate cereal. They were screaming! / 我已经给%kid1和%kid2喂过巧克力麦片了。他们在尖叫！"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/MarriageDialogueAlex",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "Indoor_Night_1": "Did you get a haircut or something? You're looking pretty good today. Maybe it's all that fresh air...$l / 你是剪头发了还是做了什么？你今天看起来气色不错。可能是因为新鲜的空气……$l",
        "fall_1": "Well, summer's over... but I'm going to stay positive. The warmer seasons will always return. / 好吧，夏天过去了……但是我要保持积极。热天总会回来的。",
        "summer_10": "Have you thought about what you're going to put in the luau soup? / 你想好在宴会的汤里面放什么了吗？#$e#I have no idea what's good... you're the chef!$h / 我不知道放什么好……你才是厨师！$h",
        "Good_0": "@... I will always love you.$l / @……我会一直爱你。$l",
        "Outdoor_3": "Look at us, with our little farm. We make a cute couple.$h / 看看我们，还有我们的小农场。我们是很配的一对。$h^Hey. Maybe it's the golden light, but you look beautiful today.$l / 嘿。可能是光线的缘故，但你今天看起来很漂亮。$l",
        "spring_6": "I wonder if a powder of stardrop would help me bulk up... / 我在想星之果实的果粉能不能帮我增强体格……",
        "Good_6": "I know you're strong, but sometimes I worry that you might get eaten by slimes... or worse. Just be careful.$9 / 我知道你很强壮，但是有时候我担心你会被史莱姆吃掉……甚至更糟糕。千万要小心。$9",
        "Indoor_Day_4": "There's a couple things around the house that I'm going to try and fix today. Don't worry about me, I'm not bored. / 我今天要处理房子里的一些事情。别担心我，我没感到厌烦。",
        "winter_7": "Are you going to enter the fishing contest tomorrow? I think you can win it! / 你要参加今年的钓鱼大赛吗？我觉得你会获胜！",
        "summer_1": "Summer's a very energetic time of year, and body feels it too! I feel solid. / 夏天是一年里最有活力的季节，而身体也会感受到！我感觉自己很结实。",
        "Indoor_Day_2": "Come here. *squeeze*... Mmhmm. You're firming up from all that farm work. / 过来。*捏紧*……唔。那些农活儿让你愈发强壮了。",
        "Indoor_Night_4": "If you need some quiet time to yourself, that's okay with me. / 如果你需要一些独处的安静时光也可以。",
        "Rainy_Night_2": "Oh... the smell? I've been eating garlic all day. I'm trying to stay manly... Sorry.$l / 噢……这个味道？我吃了一天的大蒜……我努力保持有男子气概……抱歉。$l",
        "Indoor_Night_2": "Tell me all about your day. It's good to get everything off your chest now and then. / 说说今天过得怎么样啊。时不时把自己放空也很好。",
        "Good_1": "You're very handsome... have I told you that?$l / 你很帅……我跟你说过吗？$l^You're very beautiful... have I told you that?$l / 你很美……我跟你说过吗？$l",
        "Rainy_Night_0": "Hey, did you have a good day? I'm sure tomorrow will be even better.$h / 嘿，你今天过得好吗？我相信明天会更好。$h",
        "fall_15": "Tomorrow's the fair, are we going to go? / 明天是集市，你会去吗？#$e#I don't care one way or another. / 不管怎样，我都不关心。",
        "fall_26": "I hope my grandparents are doing okay. Grandpa's too cheap to turn on the furnace until the last minute. / 希望我的祖父母一切都好。爷爷总是节俭到冷到不行的时候才把炉子打开。",
        "Rainy_Day_0": "With all this space, I can really achieve a full body workout. / 有了这么大的空间，我真的可以全身锻炼了。",
        "funLeave_Alex": "I'm going into town today. I'll see you tonight. / 今天我要到镇子里去。晚上见。",
        "Rainy_Night_4": "I was hungry so I made some dinner. Here, I saved you a plate. [241 242 225 214 198]$h / 我很饿，所以我做了晚餐。来，我为你留了一盘。 [241 242 225 214 198]$h",
        "Rainy_Day_2": "Aw... I was gonna do some jogging outside. But I can't really do it in this weather. / 啊……我本想在户外慢跑。但这种天气可不行。",
        "spring_1": "Finally, the snow has melted and the sun is back! My body feels great.$h / 终于，积雪消融，太阳又回升了！我的身体感觉很好。$h",
        "Outdoor_4": "Ahh... It feels great to be outside. Stardew Valley really is the most beautiful place... / 啊……在外面感觉可真不错！星露谷真是最美的地方……",
        "patio_Alex": "Unghh... one... Unghhh... two... It feels great to lift weights outdoors!$6 / 啊……一……啊……二……在户外举重感觉真好！$6",
        "OneKid_0": "I'm still getting used to my new life as a stay-at-home dad.$h / 我还在努力适应我居家奶爸的新生活。$h",
        "spring_23": "Oh... tomorrow's the flower dance, isn't it? I better do some extra push-ups tonight.$9 / 噢……明天是花舞节，对吧？我今晚最好多做几个俯卧撑。$9#$e#Those jumpsuits are pretty tight... and everyone's going to be watching closely. / 这些连身衣太紧了……大家都会仔细看。",
        "Outdoor_1": "This is a great place to raise children. I would've loved growing up in a place like this. So much room to run around! / 这真是抚育孩子的好地方。我喜欢在这样的地方长大。有很大的空间可以到处跑来跑去！",
        "Indoor_Day_3": "I'm still getting used to cooking and doing laundry... It's not exactly my favorite, but I knew what I was getting into when I married you.$h / 我还在努力适应做饭、洗衣服……这并不是我喜欢的，但是我知道我和你结婚之后要做这些事情。$h",
        "summer_27": "Aw... summer's almost gone. My muscles are starting to deflate...$s / 呃……夏天都要过完了。我的肌肉开始萎缩了……$s",
        "Rainy_Day_3": "*grumble*... I just woke up and I'm hungry for some protein.$9 / *嘟囔*……我刚醒，而且急需补充蛋白质。$9",
        "Rainy_Night_1": "How's it going? I've been carrying the old gridball around with me all day. A guy can pretend...$u / 怎么样了？我一天都带着那只旧格球。人可以假装……$u",
        "Indoor_Day_1": "Hey, honey! I made you a hot breakfast.[195 210 211] / 嘿，亲爱的！我给你做了热腾腾的早餐！[195 210 211]#$e#If you want to get strong, you have to eat like you mean it! / 如果你想身体强壮，那你必须把吃当做一回事！",
        "TwoKids_3": "I finally have the family life that I missed out on as a kid... thank you.$l / 我终于拥有了童年错失的家庭生活……谢谢你。$l",
        "Outdoor_0": "Hey. When I stand here and look out over our land... I'm really proud. You've done great work. / 嘿。当我站在这里，俯瞰我们的土地……我真的很骄傲。你做得真棒。",
        "Rainy_Night_3": "I've been setting aside a few scraps for Dusty. He deserves a treat now and then. / 我一直给达斯迪留些剩饭。偶尔也该对他好一点。",
        "Indoor_Day_0": "Ahh... there's nothing like a good night's sleep next to my husband!$h / 啊……在我老公旁边美美的睡一觉简直再好不过了！$h^Ahh... there's nothing like a good night's sleep next to my wife!$h / 啊……在我老婆旁边美美的睡一觉简直再好不过了！$h",
        "TwoKids_2": "Maybe %kid2 will be the first professional gridball player from Pelican Town?$h / 可能%kid2将是鹈鹕镇第一位专业格球选手？$h",
        "winter_28": "It's been a great year, @. I'm looking forward to next year! Now, come closer... $l / 真是了不起的一年，@。我很期待明年。现在，靠近一点嘛。 $l",
        "winter_1": "Make sure you stay warm this winter. I worry about your delicate skin. / 今年冬天注意保暖哦。我担心你娇嫩的皮肤。",
        "Rainy_Day_4": "I think I might start reading books. I don't want to become stagnant now that I'm a married guy! / 或许我该开始读书。既然我已经结婚了，可不能变得笨头笨脑的！",
        "Rainy_Day_1": "I never had many friends in town... I sometimes wonder how I'd end up if you never moved here.$9 / 我在镇子上的朋友从来都不多……有时候我会想如果你没搬到这里来，我会落入什么地步。$9",
        "Outdoor_2": "I like to spend as much time outside as possible. It just feels better to be out here. / 我喜欢尽可能待在外面。待在这里感觉很棒。",
        "OneKid_3": "I wonder what it's like to be pregnant...?$h / 不知道怀孕感觉怎么样？$h",
        "OneKid_1": "Little %kid1 is going to grow up strong, just like Daddy. / 小%kid1正在茁壮成长，就像他爸爸一样。",
        "spring_12": "Are you excited for tomorrow's festival? I guess it'll be good to load up on the free eggs. / 你对明天的节日感到兴奋吗？我想吃很多免费的鸡蛋对我有好处。",
        "funReturn_Alex": "I had a good day. I like to see my grandparents often, they're getting pretty old. / 我今天很愉快。我想经常看看我的祖父母，他们很老了。",
        "Indoor_Night_0": "It feels good to push yourself to the limit, doesn't it? You'll really feel like you earned your place in the soft bed tonight. / 把自己推到极限感觉很好，不是吗？今晚你会觉得在舒服的软床上有了一席之地。",
        "Indoor_Night_3": "Hey... I got some new shorts. I thought you might be interested to know...$l / 嘿……我买了些新短裤。我觉得你可能会想知道……$l"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/MarriageDialogueElliott",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "patio_Elliott": "Ah, what a lovely day to read a book... don't you think, my dear? / 啊，多么美好的适合读书的一天……亲爱的，你不觉得吗？",
        "Indoor_Night_1": "A crackling fire adds wonderful ambience to the house... every piece of wood burns in a unique way. / 噼啪的火焰给屋子增添了很棒的气氛……每块木头燃烧的方式都很独特。",
        "fall_1": "The splendor of fall... a verdant banquet for all the senses to enjoy... has inspired some of the greatest poetry of all time. / 秋天的光辉……五官的盛宴……从古至今激发了无数伟大诗人的创作灵感。",
        "Good_4": "I feel burnt out in your absence. But when I hear that sound of muddy boots on wood, my heart rises from the ash. / 你不在的时候我百爪挠心。但是当我听到森林里泥靴的声音，我的心又死灰复燃了。",
        "summer_10": "I was going to grab an extra bottle of ink from my cabin today, but then I remembered the Luau is tomorrow. I'll just do it then. / 今天我本来打算去我的屋子再拿一瓶墨水的，但是后来我想到明天就是夏威夷宴会。于是我决定到时候顺路去。",
        "Good_0": "@... I'm so proud of all your hard work. I'm very lucky to have you.$l / @……我对你的一切努力感到骄傲。有你我真幸运。$l",
        "Outdoor_3": "If I stay perfectly still, perhaps a resplendent butterfly will bless my nose with a landing. / 如果我完全待着不动，可能会有美丽的蝴蝶待在我的鼻子上不动。",
        "Good_5": "I'm doing a walking meditation. It's good for creativity. / 我正在行禅。这对激发创造力有帮助。",
        "Good_6": "Be careful out there! I do worry about you sometimes. There are people in the world who would take advantage of you. / 出去要小心啊！有时候真是担心你啊！世界上会有占你便宜的人。",
        "Indoor_Day_4": "I've had this recurring nightmare that you gave me a buzz cut... You wouldn't ever do that to me, would you?$s / 我又做了噩梦，梦到你给我剃了平头……你不会再给我剃了，对吧？$s#$e#I trust you. / 我相信你。",
        "winter_7": "I'm a little out of practice, but I plan on entering the fishing contest tomorrow! You've got some stiff competition, dear. / 我有点生疏了，但是我计划参加明天的钓鱼大赛！亲爱的，你有个强力的对手了。",
        "summer_1": "It's hard to be in a foul mood when the sun is beaming and the butterflies are dancing on a spice-berry breeze.$h / 当阳光普照，蝴蝶在充满浆果香味的微风中飞舞时，想情绪低落也难。$h",
        "Indoor_Day_2": "If you find a spider in the house, don't squash it! Just let me know and I'll take the poor thing outside. / 如果你在房子里发现蜘蛛，不要碾碎它！告诉我一声，我会把这可怜的东西丢到外面去。",
        "Indoor_Night_4": "My love... I wouldn't trade you for 100 iridium bars. / 吾爱……我不会拿100块铱锭换取你。#$e#Nor 1000... / 也不会是1000块……#$e#Not even 10,000 bars, no.$7 / 甚至10000块也不行$7#$e#...$7 / ……$7#$e#No, not even 100,000 bars!$a / 100000块也不行！$a#$e#...$s / ……$s#$e#Wa... one million bars of pure iridium...? Don't make me do this...$8 / 那……一百万块纯铱……？别让我这么做……$8",
        "Rainy_Night_2": "My skill with words is unmatched, yet I can't find the way to properly describe your allure.$l / 我很擅长写作，但我还是无法形容你的魅力。$l^My skill with words is unmatched, yet I can't find the way to properly describe your beauty.$l / 我很擅长写作，但我还是无法形容你的美。$l",
        "Indoor_Night_2": "I never had much success growing plants in my old beach house. Hopefully I can pick up a thing or two by watching you. / 我在海边的老房子里没什么成功的种植经验。希望我能跟着你学会一些技巧。#$e#In this respect, you are the master and I only a humble apprentice. / 在这方面，你是大师，而我是谦卑的学徒。",
        "Good_1": "I made a whole secret book of poems expressing my love for you.$l / 我为你写了一本秘密的诗集，来表达我对你的爱意。$l",
        "Rainy_Night_0": "Good evening. Did you have a productive day, @? / 晚上好。今天的收获如何，@？^Good evening. Did you have a productive day, my dear? / 晚上好。亲爱的，今天的收获如何？",
        "fall_15": "I might set my pride aside and sink my eager teeth into a sloppy, saucy barbecue sandwich tomorrow. / 明天我会放下我的骄傲，沉浸在松软多汁的烤三明治中。",
        "fall_26": "Would you still love me if I guzzled two gallons of pumpkin ale at the Spirit's Eve festival? Sometimes a man has primitive urges... / 如果我在万灵节上狂饮两加仑南瓜啤酒你还会爱我吗？有时候男人会有简单粗暴的欲望……",
        "funReturn_Elliott": "I had a nice time at the beach by myself. I watched the waves come and go, just like old times. / 我今天一个人在海边过得很愉快。我看潮起潮落，就像过去一样。",
        "Good_2": "I came to the valley to find the ivory tower from which my talents could reign supreme. But what I really found was a dungeon of loneliness. You saved me from that.$l / 我来到星露谷本是为了寻找能发挥我特长的象牙塔。但我却找到了孤独之牢。是你从中拯救了我。$l",
        "Rainy_Day_0": "I feel inspired today... I think I'll do some writing. / 我今天感觉有灵感……我想我会写点东西。",
        "Good_3": "Wow, you look really handsome today! Did you shave? Your jawline is perfect.$l / 哇哦，你今天看起来帅呆了！你刮胡子了吗？你的下巴轮廓堪称完美。$l^Your feminine allure is irresistible today. I can't keep my eyes off you.$l / 今天你散发的女性魅力简直让人无法抵抗。我无法将视线从你身上移开。$l",
        "Rainy_Night_4": "I spent the afternoon daydreaming about the ocean. So I decided to cook some seafood. [198 202 727 728]$h / 我一下午都在幻想大海。所以我决定煮一些海鲜。 [198 202 727 728]$h",
        "Rainy_Day_2": "I got up early and made coffee.[395] / 我起的很早，泡了些咖啡。[395]#$e#I find that a cup of this exquisite brew makes the early morning a lot more pleasant. / 我发现喝一杯这种精致的饮料能让早晨过得更加惬意！",
        "spring_1": "My new year's resolution is to write, write, and write! I can never stop improving my skills. / 我新年的决心是写作、写作、再写作！我不能停止提升我的写作技巧。",
        "Outdoor_4": "I drank too much coffee... my mouth feels about as dry as the Calico Desert.$s / 我喝太多咖啡了……我嘴巴干得像卡利科沙漠一样。$s#$e#Oh... sorry about the coffee breath.$7 / 噢……抱歉我的嘴里都是咖啡味。$7",
        "OneKid_0": "Have you had any time to entertain little %kid1 today? Maybe a second child will make things easier for both of us. / 你今天有花一点儿时间照顾小%kid1玩耍吗？可能生两个孩子会让我们更轻松些。",
        "spring_23": "I look forward to dancing with you tomorrow, my dear. / 亲爱的，我期待明天和你共舞。",
        "Outdoor_1": "Fertile soil beneath my feet, fresh air to fill my lungs, and the sun's warmth to delight my skin... Life is going well. / 肥沃的土地在我脚下，新鲜的空气充入我的肺里，温暖的太阳让我浑身舒坦……生活一切顺利。",
        "Indoor_Day_3": "Today is going to be a fantastic day... I can feel it!$h / 我有种预感……今天将会是美妙的一天！$h#$e#I get this special feeling in my nose... / 我鼻子感受到了这特别的气息……",
        "summer_27": "All good things must come to an end, including the joyful days of summer. The key to happiness is to accept change without judgment. / 所有美好的事情都会落幕，包括夏天幸福的日子。幸福的秘诀是接受改变，不去评判。",
        "Rainy_Day_3": "I think I'll remain indoors today, my dear. The rain causes my hair to go limp. / 亲爱的，我今天还是会待在屋里。这雨让我发丝柔软。",
        "Rainy_Night_1": "You're ice cold! Let me keep you warm.$l / 你身子冷冰冰的！让我帮你暖和起来吧。$l",
        "Indoor_Day_1": "Good morning, @! I made us a pot of coffee.[395] / 早上好啊，@！我泡了一壶咖啡。[395]#$e#I find myself craving this robust flavor nearly every morning. / 我发现每天早上我都贪念这强烈的味道。",
        "funLeave_Elliott": "I think I'll walk down to the beach today. It's always nice to see the ocean again. / 我想我今天会去海边。我总是很高兴再次看到大海。",
        "TwoKids_3": "We've done well, @. The farm is doing excellent and our healthy children are a great joy. I couldn't be happier. / 我们做得很好，@。农场经营得十分顺利，而我们健康的孩子也带来了巨大的喜悦。我好开心啊。",
        "Outdoor_0": "My wildest dreams have come true... just look at this incredible landscape! / 我最大的梦想实现了……看看这令人叹为观止的景色！",
        "Rainy_Night_3": "What did I do today? I'll just say this... it takes a lot of work to maintain this rugged physique! / 我今天做了什么？我要说……要花很多精力才能维持强健的体魄。",
        "Indoor_Day_0": "I've been taking much better care of myself now that we're together. The bachelor life wasn't particularly healthy for me. / 既然我们在一起了，我会更加照顾好自己的。对我来说单身生活不是很健康。",
        "TwoKids_2": "I'm going to teach %kid1 to read as soon as possible! That's a great way for children to learn about the world. / 我要尽快教%kid1看书！这是小孩了解这个世界的好方法。",
        "winter_28": "Happy new year's eve, my dear. Please accept this to celebrate. [348] / 亲爱的，除夕快乐。请收下这份庆祝礼物。[348]",
        "winter_1": "Winter is a great time to read books and play the piano. Remember to pause and enjoy a quiet moment or two. / 冬天是看书和弹钢琴的好时候。记得偶尔停下来享受安静的时光。",
        "Rainy_Day_4": "My inspiration for writing is like the weather... it comes and goes at random. Today I feel entirely dull.$s / 我写作的灵感就像天气一样……来来去去，无影无踪。今天我完全没有灵感。$s#$e#Perhaps I'll read one of the classics to get my creative juices flowing. / 也许我会读一本名著，好激发一些灵感。",
        "Rainy_Day_1": "The sound of rain, in some tiny way, reminds me of my cabin by the beach. / 雨声以一种微妙的方式让我想起我在海边的小屋。#$e#The farm is wonderful, but I do miss the sound of the ocean. / 农场很棒，但是我还是想念大海的声音。",
        "Outdoor_2": "I might stay here and write some poetry. I'm feeling a sudden surge of creativity! You go on ahead and take care of business. / 我可能会待在这里，写一些诗。我感觉灵感突然涌来。你继续，看好生意。",
        "OneKid_3": "Caring for babies isn't exactly my strong suit... but I'll do my best to be a good father. / 照顾孩子不是我的强项……但我会尽我最大的努力做个好爸爸。",
        "OneKid_1": "Little %kid1 is going to have the perfect childhood here. There's so much to explore. / 小%kid1将在这里度过快乐的童年。有好多可以探索的地方。",
        "spring_12": "It's strange, but I often have cravings for pomegranate in the spring. / 这很奇怪，但是我春天经常渴望吃石榴。",
        "Indoor_Night_0": "From the brightest winter star, to the shimmer of an iridium vein... nothing can compare to my wonderful man.$l / 从最闪亮的冬日之星到铱矿的微光，都不比不上我的好人儿。$l^From the brightest winter star, to the fragrant fairy rose... nothing can compare with your captivating beauty.$l / 从最闪亮的冬日之星到铱矿的微光，都不比不上你迷人的美。$l",
        "TwoKids_0": "I already gave %kid1 and %kid2 their food. They eat a lot for such small creatures! / 我已经给%kid1和%kid2喂过饭了。小东西们吃了很多！",
        "TwoKids_1": "I was carrying %kid1 earlier, and I could've sworn I heard a \"Da...da\".$h / 我之前带过%kid1，我发誓我听到了“爸……爸”的声音。$h",
        "Indoor_Night_3": "When I behold thy wondrous face, a precious jewel of form and grace, my heart... torn by the dread of night, is purified with golden light. / 当我注视你美妙的脸庞，金色的光净化了我那颗被恐怖的黑夜撕裂的心。#$e#Poetry is the only way I can begin to describe my feelings for you.$l / 只有诗才能描述我对你的感觉。$l"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/MarriageDialogueEmily",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "Indoor_Night_1": "Welcome home, @. I hope you had a wonderful day. / 欢迎回家，@。希望你今天过得很愉快。",
        "spring_22": "Hmm... I'm thinking maybe a salad of fresh foraged greens for dinner tonight? / 嗯……我想可以用新摘的蔬菜做一个沙拉，作为晚餐，怎么样？",
        "spring_Emily": "I'm feeling excited for a new year of farming, @!$h / 新的一年耕种开始了，我好兴奋啊，@！$h",
        "fall_1": "The year's already half-way over. Can you believe it? / 今年已经过去一半了。真是难以置信！",
        "Good_4": "Our vibrational energies are perfectly in tune. Can't you feel it? / 我们的振动能量极为协调。你能感觉到吗？",
        "Outdoor_3": "A little sunlight is good for you. Just don't get crispy, okay? / 晒一晒太阳对你是有好处的。不要感到不爽，好吗？",
        "winter_2": "I can't help but think of all the poor, frozen squirrels out there right now.$s / 我不禁想到那些正在外面冻得瑟瑟发抖的可怜的松鼠们。$s",
        "Neutral_0": "I hope you'll still like me when I grow old and my hair turns to a dull, faded steel. / 当我老了，头发变白、变硬的时候，我希望你会依然喜欢我。",
        "Good_5": "I was just admiring my wedding amulet... The shell is beautiful! I can feel the pure blue energy radiating from it.$l / 我十分欣赏我的婚礼护身符……这外形真漂亮！我能感觉到从它身上散发出来的纯蓝能量。$l",
        "Good_6": "I had another dream about us last night. We had climbed to the top of a crystal tree, looking down on the most lush and beautiful meadow. I keep having this dream. / 昨晚我又做了一个关于我们梦。我们爬到了一棵水晶树顶上，看着茂盛的和美丽的草地。我一直在做这个梦。#$e#I don't know what it means, but I feel that it's a good omen. / 我不知道这意味着什么，但我觉得这是一个好兆头。",
        "Indoor_Day_4": "Ughh... *gurgle*... I ate too many bran muffins for breakfast.$s / 啊……*嗝*……我早餐吃了太多的麸皮松饼。$s",
        "Indoor_Day_2": "Hey, someone must've gotten a good night of sleep... you look fresh this morning.$h / 嘿，某人一定睡得很好……今天早上你看上去很清新亮丽。$h",
        "Indoor_Night_4": "I swept the whole house, washed the windows, dusted, and cleaned the fridge. It was a very productive day! / 我打扫了整个屋子，擦洗了窗户，并清理了冰箱。真是非常充实的一天！",
        "winter_15": "On a day like this, I have a craving for cinnamon, nutmeg, clove, and cardamom. / 在这样的日子里，我渴望得到肉桂、肉豆蔻、丁香、小豆蔻。",
        "winter_Emily": "Whoops, my hair is frozen solid again.$s / 哎呦，我的头发又凝固了。$s",
        "fall_Emily": "I drank a super-food smoothie this morning and I feel aaah-mazing!$h / 今天早上我喝了营养奶昔，感觉超超超——超棒的！$h",
        "Rainy_Night_2": "How was your day, @? You look a little soggy. / 你今天怎么样？你看起来有点儿闷闷不乐。@",
        "Indoor_Night_2": "Is it bed time already? My, the day just floated away from me again.$u / 已经到睡觉时间了？哎呀，又一天从我身边飘走了。$u",
        "Good_1": "This is so fun to live together! I always thought I'd be single my whole life. / 生活在一起原来如此有趣！我一直以为我会单身一辈子。",
        "summer_Emily": "Phew! It's hot but it feels great, doesn't it? / 咻！很热，但感觉很好，不是吗？#$e#Maybe we'll see some wild parrots today. / 也许今天我们会看到一些野生鹦鹉。",
        "Rainy_Night_0": "Every moment has a unique and precious beauty... do you notice? It can be easy to forget, sometimes. / 每一个时刻都有一种独特而珍贵的美丽……你注意到了吗？有时它很容易被忽略。",
        "Good_2": "It was our destiny to be together... I believe that with all my heart! / 我们走到一起是命中注定……我真心相信这一点！",
        "Rainy_Day_0": "I wonder where the flying insects go when it rains? Don't they get hit by the raindrops? / 我想知道下雨时飞虫都到哪里去了？雨水难道不会打在它们身上吗？",
        "Good_3": "Thanks for taking me into your home. I love this new life.$4 / 谢谢你带我到你的家。我喜欢这个新的生活。$4",
        "summer_20": "The energy in our bodies fluctuate just as the seasons do. Understanding your own unique rhythm is the first step to inner harmony. / 我们体内的能量就像季节一样在波动。了解你自己独有的节奏是通往内在和谐的第一步。",
        "Rainy_Night_4": "Want some dessert? It's my special raw, gluten-free version, sweetened only with cactus syrup.[232 234 223 220]$h / 来一些甜点吗？这是我用特殊原料做的，不含麸质，只用仙人掌糖浆来增加甜味。[232 234 223 220]$h",
        "Rainy_Day_2": "Good morning... I got this gift for you. Don't worry, I already purified it with sage incense. [428 440 444 338 207] / 早上好……这是我为你准备的礼物。不要担心，我已经用熏香熏过了。[428 440 444 338 207]",
        "spring_1": "Happy new year, honey. Let's make this a special one.$4 / 新年快乐，宝贝。让我们把这一年过得特别一点。$4",
        "summer_2": "May Yoba bless you on this lovely day.$7 / 在这美好的一天，愿由巴保佑你。$7",
        "funLeave_Emily": "I'm going to visit town today, and later on I'm going to help out at the saloon. Have a nice day. / 今天我打算去镇上逛逛，然后去酒吧帮忙。祝你有美好的一天。",
        "Outdoor_4": "Good morning! I was wondering when you'd finally roll out of bed!$h / 早上好！我还在想你什么时候才会起床呢！$h#$e#It's okay, @... you deserve a good night of rest. / 没关系，@……你应该好好睡上一晚。",
        "OneKid_0": "I hope we can raise %kid1 to be kind and considerate. That's more important than getting A's in school. / 我希望我们的孩子%kid1能拥有善良和体贴的品质。这比在学校得高分重要多了。",
        "Outdoor_1": "What's on the agenda today, dear? / 今天的日程是什么，亲爱的？",
        "Indoor_Day_3": "My horoscope for the day isn't too good... but I'm going to make the best of it, as always. Let's get to work! / 我的星座运势今天不是太好……但是仍将尽量努力。让我们开始工作吧！",
        "Neutral_8": "I feel uninspired today.$s / 我今天没有灵感……$s",
        "spring_2": "My friends, the plants, have come back to life. I feel content. / 我的植物朋友们都重新焕发出了生机。我感到很满足。",
        "funReturn_Emily": "My day went well... it's good to get out of the house now and then. / 我今天过得很好……偶尔出去走走也挺好的。",
        "spouseRoom_Emily": "I'm going to spend some time with the parrot today. It breaks my heart that he'll never fly again.$u / 我今天将花一些时间陪伴鹦鹉。它永远也不会飞了，真令我伤心。$u",
        "Rainy_Day_3": "I meant to let the parrot go free, but his wing never fully healed. He seems content, though. I give him lots of attention. / 我本来打算放飞这只鹦鹉，但是它的翅膀总是无法痊愈。不过它看起来很满足。我经常照顾它。#$e#He told me that he's happy here. / 它对我说在这里很快乐。",
        "Rainy_Night_1": "I can hear the plants talking to each other... they're so happy after today's rain! / 我能听到植物彼此的交谈……今天下雨过后他们很开心！",
        "fall_25": "Our bodies are naturally in tune with the seasons. This light and color of fall compels us to prepare for the barren winter. / 我们的身体自然地与季节保持一致。秋天的光线和色彩迫使我们为荒凉的冬季做准备。#$e#To our distant ancestors, this feeling was encompassing and vital. For us, it only barely peeks through the noise of modern life. / 对于我们远古的祖先来说，这种感觉一直伴随着他们并且至关重要。对于我们来说，它仅仅是透过喧嚣的现代生活轻轻一瞥而已。",
        "Indoor_Day_1": "Here, take this. It's for you. [428 440 444 338 207 395 749] / 来，拿着。这是给你的。[428 440 444 338 207 395 749]",
        "patio_Emily": "This is my favorite spot for a morning meditation. / 这是我清晨冥想时最喜欢来的地方。#$e#I visualize the energy from this crystal garden flowing through my body. / 我想象这座水晶花园中的能量流经我的身体。",
        "Outdoor_0": "I love getting up early. There's a certain freshness to the air and the wildlife is much more active. / 我喜欢早起。空气比较清新，自然界中的生命也更有活力。",
        "Rainy_Night_3": "My day was very peaceful. How was yours? / 我的一天非常平静。你的呢？",
        "Indoor_Day_0": "Another beautiful day on %farm farm... I have faith that something good will happen today!$h / 在%farm农场的又一个美好的一天……我相信今天会有好事发生！$h",
        "TwoKids_2": "Well, %kid2 certainly has your hair...$u / 嗯，%kid2的头发确实像你……$u",
        "TwoKids_3": "Oh, I already fed the kids their organic quinoa puffs with goat milk. You just focus on the farm! / 噢，我已经给孩子喂过羊奶和有机藜麦泡芙了。你专心照顾农场就好！",
        "Rainy_Day_4": "I never told you this... but when you first moved here I had a dream about you. I knew right then that our life-paths would intertwine.$4 / 我从来没有告诉过你……但是当你第一次来到这里时，我做了一个跟你有关的梦。我就知道我们的人生道路会交织在一起。$4",
        "Rainy_Day_1": "A day like this is a blessing from mother nature. / 像这样的一天是来自大自然的祝福。",
        "winter_5": "*sigh*... Why does there have to be war and hatred in the world?$s / *唉*……为什么世界上有战争和仇恨呢？$s",
        "Outdoor_2": "Oooh! Ooh! I saw another one!$h / 哦哦！哦！我又看到一只了！$h#$e#I'm counting squirrels. / 我正在数松鼠。",
        "OneKid_3": "I lit a pale green candle and shook a sprig of baby-mint over %kid1. That should ward off any dangerous spirits. / 我点燃了一只浅绿色的蜡烛，并在%kid1头上抖了抖一束嫩薄荷枝。这样应该能驱走任何危险的幽灵。",
        "Rainy_Night_5": "Does the sound of rain ever put you in a trance? / 雨声会不会让你听到入迷？",
        "OneKid_1": "Is one child enough, or should we raise another? / 一个孩子够吗，或者我们再生一个？#$e#I guess we'll just see where fate leads us. / 我想我们还是看命运的安排吧。",
        "Indoor_Night_0": "Is that a new hole I see in your shirt? I can sew that up for you, no problem. / 你的衬衫上是不是又破了个洞？不用担心，我可以给你缝上。",
        "TwoKids_1": "A big house, two kids and a parrot... I have my hands full! / 一个大房子，两个孩子和一只鹦鹉……我忙得不可开交！",
        "Indoor_Night_3": "Ah, that aroma! It can only be you.$h / 啊，那个香味！只有你会散发出这种香味。$h#$e#It's a good smell. / 真好闻。"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/MarriageDialogueHaley",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "funReturn_Haley": "It was nice seeing everyone in town. Did you have a good day, dear? / 在镇子里看到大家真好。你今天过得好吗？",
        "Indoor_Night_Haley": "You look like you've been working hard, dear. Let me help you de-stress.$l / 亲爱的，你看起来干了不少活啊。让我帮你减减压。$l",
        "fall_1": "Fall is kind of sad for me... everything is dying.$5 / 对我来说秋天令人悲伤……一切都在消亡。$5",
        "spring_Haley": "Aren't you glad winter's over, honey? Things seem more hopeful now. / 甜心，冬天结束了你不开心吗？现在一切又充满了希望。",
        "Outdoor_3": "I'm just going to do some dusting over here. That should help you out, right? / 我就在这扫扫灰。这会帮到你吧？#$e#*phew*... it's hot out here. / *呼*……这儿还真热啊。",
        "winter_2": "For some reason, the snowy weather gives me cravings for pink cake... / 由于某些原因，下雪天让我渴望吃粉红色的蛋糕……",
        "Indoor_Day_4": "Good morning, dear. Another day of farm chores, huh? / 亲爱的，早上好。一天的农活又开始了吧？#$e#I'll be thinking of you. <$h / 我会一直想着你的。<$h",
        "Indoor_Day_2": "Did you sleep okay? You were snoring a little.$h / 睡得还好吗？你有点儿打鼾。$h#$e#I've got some chores to do in here. Have a good day. / 我还要做些家务。祝你今天愉快。",
        "Rainy_Night_2": "I hope Emily isn't too lonely all by herself. I should visit her again soon.$7 / 我希望艾米丽一个人的时候不会太孤独。我应该尽快再去看她的。$7",
        "Rainy_Night_0": "Oh, I'm glad you're back. It's so cold in here by myself... Are you almost ready to shut off the lights? / 噢，我很高兴你回来了。我一个人在这儿的时候感觉太冷了……你准备好关灯了吗？",
        "winter_14": "My skin feels so dry in this weather. / 在这种天气，我皮肤很干燥。",
        "Rainy_Day_0": "I've changed a lot over the years, but I still prefer sunny weather. / 多年来我已经变了很多，但我还是更喜欢晴天。",
        "summer_15": "It's summer... that means the house is full of flies and ants... yuck.$s / 现在是夏天了……意味着房子里都是苍蝇和蚂蚁……真恶心。$s",
        "summer_3": "Sorry if I don't look my best... the air is just so humid that my hair doesn't hold up too well. / 抱歉我的样子可能不太好看……空气太湿了，我头发都塌下去了。",
        "Rainy_Night_4": "I made a hot meal for you, honey. Lots of spice, just how you like it. Enjoy! [727 231 207 199]$h / 亲爱的，我为你做了一顿热饭。按你喜欢的口味加了许多香料。尽情享用吧。 [727 231 207 199]$h",
        "Rainy_Day_2": "Good morning! I got up early and baked something sweet for you! [223 234 211 651 731] / 早啊！我今天起得早，给你烤了些甜点！[223 234 211 651 731]#$e#I know you're strong, but you still need to eat well to stay at your best!$h / 我知道你身体强壮，但还是要吃得好点儿，保持最佳状态！$h",
        "spring_1": "Now that winter's over, we've got lots of sunny weather to look forward to. I'm excited. / 冬天过去了，接下来会有很多阳光明媚的天气。我好期待呀。",
        "Outdoor_4": "Don't overwork yourself, dear. / 亲爱的，别累着自己了。#$e#Make sure and take a break every now and then, or get something to eat.$h / 记得不时地休息一下，或者吃点东西。$h",
        "funLeave_Haley": "I'm going to socialize in town for a bit today. / 今天我要去镇子里玩一会儿。",
        "Outdoor_1": "We've got to make sure the farm is cute! That might be important... right, honey? / 我们要让农场很吸引人。那很重要……对吧，亲爱的？",
        "Outdoor_Haley": "Looks like a good day to work on my tan, don't you think, sweetheart? / 甜心，你不觉得今天是个晒太阳的好日子吗？",
        "Indoor_Day_3": "I'm glad I've learned to enjoy cleaning! The house gets dirty very easily.$10 / 我很高新自己学着享受打扫！房子很容易变脏。$10#$e#It's satisfying to get everything squeaky clean. / 把所有东西清理好是件让人有成就感的事。#$e#Can I have a kiss before you leave?$11 / 在你走之前我能吻你吗？$11",
        "spring_2": "So, what are we planting this season? / 话说，这个季度我们种些什么呢？",
        "Rainy_Day_3": "I can't go outside today... my hair will go limp. Forgive me, dear.$s / 今天我不能出去了……我头发会变软的。亲爱的，原谅我。$s#$e#I want to look my best for you. / 我想向你展示我最好的一面。",
        "Rainy_Night_1": "I hope it's nice and sunny tomorrow morning. Too much rain can make me moody.$s / 我希望明天上午阳光明媚。一直下雨会让我郁闷的。$s",
        "Indoor_Day_1": "Good morning, dear! Smells good, doesn't it? I made you breakfast! [194 195 210 211 216] / 亲爱的，早上好。是不是有很香的味道？我给你做了早餐！[194 195 210 211 216]#$e#I know you're busy with your work. I'm here to support you in any way I can! / 我知道你工作很忙。我会尽力支持你。",
        "TwoKids_3": "A big house, two kids, and a beautiful plot of land. I'm not sure what else I could ask for. / 一栋大房子，两个孩子还有一方美丽的土地。我不知道我还想要什么。",
        "Outdoor_0": "I always feel best when I'm outside, breathing fresh air. / 我在外面呼吸新鲜空气的时候总是感觉很好。#$b#Don't get me wrong, your grandpa's old cottage is very nice! But nothing beats this beautiful landscape. / 别误会我，你爷爷的老农舍很不错！但什么都不比不上这里美丽的风景。",
        "Rainy_Night_3": "Rain is horrible for a photographer. The lighting is awful, and you can't go outside without ruining your equipment!$s / 下雨对摄影师来说太讨厌了。光线糟透了，而且一出门准会毁了设备！$s",
        "Indoor_Day_0": "Good morning! Did you sleep well?$h / 早啊！睡得还好吗？$h#$e#I think I might break out the old camera today... the lighting is just perfect. / 我想我今天可能把老相机拿出来用……光线实在是太完美啦。",
        "TwoKids_2": "Isn't %kid2 a very good-looking baby? / %kid2可真是个漂亮的宝贝呀！",
        "Rainy_Night_Haley": "Hi, honey. I'm so glad you're home. I was starting to get kind of lonely.$l / 嗨，甜心！真高兴你回来了。我都有点孤单了。$l",
        "Rainy_Day_4": "Are you going out in this weather? Just make sure to wipe your boots on the way back in, honey. / 这种天气你要出去吗？亲爱的，在进来的时候把靴子擦干净。#$e#I'll just stay here and do some housework. / 我会待在这里，做些家务。",
        "fall_2": "I already miss summer... / 我已经开始怀念夏天了……",
        "Rainy_Day_1": "Sometimes I daydream about our retirement... relaxing on the sunny beaches of the Fern Islands! / 有时候我会幻想我们的退休生活……在芬群岛的阳光沙滩上放松！#$e#Do you ever think about the future, @? / 你想过未来吗，@？",
        "winter_Haley": "I was just thinking about the time you helped me open a jar of pickles. Remember that?$h / 我又回想起你帮我开咸菜罐头的那一天。还记得吗？$h#$e#We've come a long way since then.$l / 我们也是在那之后好上的。$l",
        "patio_Haley": "Say 'goat cheese'! / 说“山羊奶酪”！",
        "Outdoor_2": "Hi, honey! If I knew more about farm work I'd help you out more. Sorry! / 嗨，甜心！要是我多懂些耕种的知识，我一定会多帮帮你的。对不起！#$e#I'll be thinking of you.$h / 我会一直想着你的。$h",
        "Rainy_Day_Haley": "Oh no... If this weather keeps up I'll get so pale.$s / 糟了……这天气再这么下去，皮肤都要变成惨白色了。$s",
        "OneKid_3": "Isn't it strange? I'm not used to being a mother. / 不觉得很奇怪吗？我还不习惯当个母亲。",
        "Rainy_Night_5": "I never thought I'd say this, but the country lifestyle really suits me.$h / 我从没想过我会这么说，但是乡村生活真的很适合我。$h",
        "summer_Haley": "I love watching the fireflies on a hot summer's night. It's the closest I'll ever come to visiting the stars. / 我喜欢夏天晚上看萤火虫……那是我最接近星星的时候。",
        "Indoor_Day_Haley": "I felt like I had no direction in life before I met you. Now I have exactly what I want.$l / 我觉得在遇到你之前我的人生没有方向。现在我知道自己到底想要什么了。$l",
        "fall_Haley": "Even though I prefer summer, fall might be the best season to take pictures. Those long, low shadows... / 尽管我更喜欢夏天，但是秋天可能是最适合摄影的季节。那些长长的阴影……"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/MarriageDialogueHarvey",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "Indoor_Night_1": "I took it easy today... spent some time reading books, fiddled with my radio, and worked on a model airplane. / 我今天很放松……看了会儿书、听了会儿收音机，并玩了会儿飞机模型。#$e#It's important to take a day off now and then to relax... stress is unhealthy. / 不时休息放松一下很重要……压力有害健康。",
        "fall_1": "Make sure and diversify your harvests this fall, my dear. / 亲爱的，今年秋天多种几种作物。#$e#Or just grow cranberries... It's really up to you. What do I know? / 或者只种蔓越莓……这取决于你。我懂什么呢？",
        "summer_10": "Have you thought about what you're going to put in the luau soup? / 你想好在宴会的汤里面放什么了吗？#$e#I would put an item of high value and quality. We all want to leave a great impression on the governor! / 我会放一种高价值、高质量的东西。我们都想给州长留下深刻印象！",
        "Good_0": "@...I still can't believe we're married...$l / @……我还是不敢相信我们结婚了……$l",
        "Outdoor_3": "@... you... you mean the world to me.$l / @……你……你对我来说就是整个世界。$l",
        "Good_6": "Be careful out there! I have nightmares about your limp body being wheeled into the emergency room.$7 / 出去要小心啊！我做了噩梦，梦到你柔弱的身体被推进急诊室。$7",
        "Indoor_Day_4": "I was afraid of you when we first met. It's funny to think about now that we've come so far.$h / 我们第一次见面的时候我有点怕你。现在想想我们居然走到了今天，还真有趣。$h",
        "winter_7": "Are we going to stop by the ice festival tomorrow? I do enjoy the igloos... / 明天我们要顺便路过冰雪节吗？我很喜欢圆顶建筑……",
        "funReturn_Harvey": "I had a nice day. It's refreshing to spend some time alone now and then. Did you have a good day, honey? / 我今天很愉快。不时独处一下让人神清气爽。你今天过得好吗，亲爱的？",
        "summer_1": "Make sure you don't get sunburnt, dear! It's very dangerous for your skin.$8 / 千万别晒伤了，亲爱的！那对你的皮肤来说很危险。$8#$e#As your husband and doctor, I consider your health and safety my top priority! / 作为你的丈夫和医生，你的健康和安全是我第一优先考虑的事情！",
        "patio_Harvey": "You know, this 'journal of tendon dynamics' is actually bearable when I'm reading out here. / 你要知道，当我在这里阅读的时候，这本《肌腱动力学》杂志实际上还是可以看得下去的。",
        "Indoor_Day_2": "I'm going to study the medical literature today. It's important for me to keep up-to-date so I can give my patients the best care possible! / 今天我要研究医学文献。对我来说跟上最新趋势很重要，这样我才能为我的患者提供最好的护理！",
        "Indoor_Night_4": "Oh! I was just daydreaming about the circulatory system and forgot what I was trying to do. It's a classic doctor's problem. / 噢！我只是在思考着循环系统，而忘了我要去做什么。这是医生典型的问题。",
        "Rainy_Night_2": "You look a little soggy, hun. Why don't you warm yourself by the fire? / 你看起来打湿了一点呀？为何不在火边烤暖和一点？^You look a little soggy, dear. Why don't you warm yourself by the fire? / 亲爱的，你看起来打湿了一点？为何不在火边烤暖和一点？",
        "Indoor_Night_2": "Good evening... did you finish everything you needed to do today? / 晚上好……你完成了今天要做的事情了吗？#$e#Don't worry about me. I'm very self-sufficient. If you have more work to do go right ahead. / 不要担心我。我很独立。如果你有更多事情要做，那就请便吧。",
        "Good_1": "You rescued me from a life of loneliness, and filled the emptiness in my heart. Thank you.$l / 你把我从孤独的生活中拯救出来，填补了我心里的空缺。谢谢你。$l",
        "Rainy_Night_0": "How was your day, honey? I was going to do the dishes but I got absorbed in the latest issue of \"Knee Surgery Enthusiast\". / 亲爱的，今天过得怎么样？我今天本打算洗盘子的，但结果沉迷于阅读最新一期“膝盖手术爱好者”了。",
        "fall_15": "Tomorrow's the fair. The food is very rich and salty, but I'm fine with splurging once in a while.$h / 明天是集市。食物丰富而且很咸，但我偶尔也可以奢侈一下。$h",
        "fall_26": "I'll admit, the spirit's eve festival usually gives me intestinal pain... but I'll do my best to be brave. / 我承认，万灵节总是让我肠痛……但是我会尽量勇敢的。",
        "Good_2": "I knew you were the one from the moment you moved here...$l / 自从你搬到这里，我就知道你是我的命中注定……$l",
        "Rainy_Day_0": "It's a myth that rainy weather causes the flu. However, take care that you don't slip on the mud! / 雨天会引起流感是个谬论。但是，注意不要在泥里滑倒了！#$e#I often worry about you. / 我常常很担心你。",
        "Good_3": "Wow, you look really handsome today! Did you shave?$l / 哇哦，你今天看起来帅呆了！你刮胡子了吗？$l^Oh, my... you look beautiful today.$l / 哇哦……你今天看起来美极了。$l",
        "Rainy_Night_4": "I made us a nice healthy dinner. Only fresh, wholesome ingredients from the valley! [212 214 225 209 200]$h / 我做了一顿美美的健康晚餐。都是谷里新鲜、有益健康的食材！[212 214 225 209 200]$h#$e#Just make sure to eat a reasonable portion, dear. / 亲爱的，好吃也不要贪多哦。",
        "Rainy_Day_2": "I woke up early, but I made sure not to wake you. You looked so peaceful. / 我醒得很早，但是我不会吵醒你的。你看起来很平静。",
        "spring_1": "It's wonderful to see all the plants return to life. The greenery is refreshing after a monochrome winter. / 看到万物复苏真是好啊！单调的冬天过后植物都焕然一新了。",
        "Outdoor_4": "As a scientist I'm fascinated by the delicate interplay of insect and plant life. / 作为一名科学家，我对昆虫和植物微妙的相互作用很着迷。",
        "OneKid_0": "You and %kid1 are the most important parts of my life. / 你和%kid1是我生命中最重要的部分。",
        "spring_23": "W...Will you dance with me at the festival tomorrow?$7 / 你……你明天会和我跳舞吗？$7#$e#It's always a little embarrassing.$7 / 这总是有点尴尬。$7",
        "Outdoor_1": "I believe this must be the ideal place to raise children, scientifically. What do you think? / 从科学上来讲，我想在这里抚养孩子十分理想。你认为如何？",
        "Indoor_Day_3": "I'm going to listen to some jazz music and finalize my medical reports today. What do you have planned? / 今天我要听爵士乐，并完成我的医疗报告。你有什么计划？",
        "summer_27": "As summer draws to a close, and the colder season begins, my workload tends to increase. Sorry in advance if I'm a little moody... / 随着夏天即将结束，冷天即将开始，我的工作量也开始增加。如果我有点儿郁郁寡欢，那我提前说声抱歉……",
        "Rainy_Day_3": "I don't mind the rain. Sure, I can't watch the planes go by, but I can still listen to the radio chatter. / 我不介意下雨。当然，我看不到飞机经过，但我还是能听到收音机的吱吱声。#$e#It makes the whole thing a little more mysterious. / 它让所有事物都更加神秘了。",
        "Rainy_Night_1": "If you're enjoying life, who cares if it's a little repetitive? That's what I say. / 如果你享受生活，又怎么会介意生活的重复琐碎？我是这么说的。",
        "Indoor_Day_1": "Good morning, @! I made you a nutritious breakfast.[201] / 早上好啊，@！我给你做了营养早餐！[201]#$e#Eggs are a good source of essential nutrients, so eat up. / 鸡蛋是很好的蛋白质来源，都吃掉吧。",
        "TwoKids_3": "My life is devoted to you and the children now, and I'm very happy about it. I always dreamed of having a wonderful family.$l / 现在我深爱着你和孩子们，并且我很幸福。我一直梦想着有个美满的家庭。$l#$e#I had nightmares of being a bachelor forever.... I love you so much.$l / 我害怕一直单身……我好爱你。$l",
        "Outdoor_0": "This is a very safe spot. You go on ahead and take care of business, don't worry about me. / 这是个很安全的地点。你继续去忙吧，不要担心我。",
        "Rainy_Night_3": "The sound of rain gives our minds something to focus on, so we're not distracted by random thoughts. / 雨声让我们的注意力集中在一些事上，所以不会因为胡思乱想分散注意力。#$e#That's my theory for why it's so soothing... / 这是我认为为什么雨天让人宽慰的理由……",
        "Indoor_Day_0": "I think we're all striving to reach some kind of balance in life. An equilibrium of complexity. / 我想我们都在努力达到生活的某种平衡。一种复杂的平衡。#$e#For me, moving here was exactly what my body needed to find that balance.$l / 对我来说，搬到这里正适合我找到那种平衡。$l",
        "TwoKids_2": "Maybe %kid2 will grow up to become a pilot, like I never could? / 或许%kid2长大以后可能会成为一名飞行员，像我永远不能企及的那样？",
        "winter_28": "Well, here's to a fantastic year. I have complete confidence that next year will be even better!$h / 嗯，今年真是美妙的一年。我完全相信明年会更好！$h",
        "winter_1": "The air is very dry during winter. That's why our skin tends to become irritated. / 冬天的时候空气很干燥。所以我皮肤会发红。#$e#Don't worry, I'll rub a little truffle oil onto your back every night.$l / 别担心，每天晚上我会在你的背上擦一些松露油。$l",
        "Rainy_Day_4": "I have a backlog of house chores I want to complete today. I've got plenty to keep me busy! / 我积了一堆的家务，今天想全部弄完。我有好多事情要忙呢！",
        "Rainy_Day_1": "It was so incredibly lonely living above the clinic by myself... I'm much happier now.$h / 我一个人住在诊所上面简直孤独得无以复加……现在我开心多了。$h",
        "Outdoor_2": "I may not be the most exciting guy, but I'll stay loyal to you for the rest of my life.$l / 我可能不是最令人激动的人，但是我余生都会对你忠诚。$l",
        "OneKid_3": "So far, I really like being a father!$h / 我真喜欢当父亲的感觉！$h",
        "funLeave_Harvey": "I think I'll take a little walk today. I need to unwind. / 我想今天稍稍散一下步。我需要放松一下。",
        "OneKid_1": "Little %kid1 is going to have the perfect childhood here. We're really fortunate to have this opportunity. / 小%kid1将在这里度过快乐的童年。我们有这个机会真幸运。",
        "spring_12": "Oh, it's a festival tomorrow, isn't it? Large crowds, activities... *gulp*$s / 噢，明天有个节庆，对吧？人群、活动……*吞口水* ……$s",
        "Indoor_Night_0": "You look exhausted, dear. Let me give you a massage tonight. I promise it will reduce the inflammation in your muscle tissue!$l / 亲爱的，你看起来精疲力尽。让我今晚给你按摩吧。我保证这会减轻你肌肉组织的炎症！$l",
        "TwoKids_0": "I already gave %kid1 and %kid2 their breakfasts. I'm trying to teach them to enjoy healthy food! / 我已经给%kid1和%kid2喂过早餐了。我试着教他们享用健康的食物！",
        "TwoKids_1": "I believe a child should be allowed to play and explore to their heart's content. You're only a kid once. / 我认为应该允许孩子随意探索与玩耍。毕竟你只有一个童年。",
        "Indoor_Night_3": "It's stressful to be a doctor, so it's really great to live somewhere as relaxing as %farm Farm. / 当医生很有压力，所以住在像%farm农场一样放松的地方真是太棒了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/MarriageDialogueKrobus",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "Bad_6": "You only have one short life to live... are you certain you want to spend it with a hideous creature like me?$s / 你只有短暂的一生……你确定要和我这种可怖的生物度过它吗？$s",
        "winter_12": "... / ……",
        "Indoor_Night_1": "You feel solid... sometimes I wish I had bones, too...$s / 你很结实的样子……有时我也会想，要是我也有骨头就好了……$s",
        "Bad_2": "Are you still happy, living with me?$s / 你和我一起生活还开心吗？$s",
        "Bad_8": "You seem unhappy lately...$s / 你最近看起来挺丧气的……$s",
        "Neutral_0": "I won't ever grow old, but you will. Sometimes it makes me sad... but that's okay.$s / 我不会变老，但是你会。有时这会让我有点伤感……不过也不是什么大事。$s",
        "Good_5": "I was just admiring this lovely house... what a wonderful place.$l / 我刚刚只是在欣赏这间可爱的屋子……真是个好地方。$l",
        "winter_Krobus": "The darkness this time of year is very soothing. If only it were warmer! / 这个时节天气阴沉，令人心神镇定。要是能暖和一点就好了！",
        "Rainy_Day_Krobus": "Ah, it's more humid today with the rain... I feel a lot more comfortable. / 啊，今天下了雨，空气更潮湿了……我感觉更加舒服了。",
        "summer_1": "I get sunburnt very easily, so I need to be careful this time of year. / 我很容易晒伤，所以这个季节得小心。",
        "spring_19": "... / ……",
        "Indoor_Day_2": "I'm happy here, in the house. I like to spend all my time in a good spot... I don't need to \"get out\" like humans do. / 我在屋子里很开心。我喜欢在一个好地方呆很久……我没有人类“出门”的需要。#$e#But I understand that you need to! Please don't feel like you have to stay here with me.$3 / 不过我理解你需要出门的！不用非得一直和我呆在一起，没事的。$3",
        "Neutral_5": "Welwick says I'm cursed today.$s / 维尔维克说我今天被诅咒了。$s",
        "Indoor_Night_4": "I want to be a good housemate for you, but I never know if I'm doing well... *groan* $s / 我想尽可能好地与你同居，但是我不知道我做的是不是够好……（咕哝）$s#$e#I have a hard time understanding human expression. B... but... you're happy living with me? / 想要理解人类的表达挺难的。不……不过……你和我一起住觉得开心吗？#$e#Okay!$7 / 好的！$7",
        "Rainy_Night_2": "You're sopping wet, and cold! Isn't that dangerous to your species?$s / 你湿透了，还冰凉冰凉的！这对你们的种族来说不是很危险吗？$s",
        "fall_5": "... / ……",
        "Rainy_Night_0": "On nights like this, those who gaze out windows sometimes see shadowy figures. To think... it might've been me.$7 / 在这样的夜晚，向窗外眺望的人有时会看见影子一样的人形。仔细想想……大概是我吧。$7",
        "fall_26": "... / ……",
        "summer_15": "It's summer... that means the house is full of flies. / 到夏天了……于是屋子里会有很多苍蝇。#$e#Don't worry, I'll take care of them. It's good protein!$h / 别担心，我会处理掉的。这可是优质蛋白！$h",
        "summer_19": "... / ……",
        "summer_8": "Mmm... what's that lovely smell? You must've been sweating all night...$h / 嗯……这香味是什么？你肯定一晚上都在出汗吧……$h",
        "Good_3": "You started nibbling on me during the night, and mumbling about 'black lick or ish'... what did you mean by that?$3 / 你晚上的时候开始啃我，嘴里还咕哝着“黑甘炒糖”……那是什么意思？$3",
        "Bad_7": "Maybe a relationship like this is destined to fail...$s / 也许这样的关系注定是要失败的……$s",
        "Rainy_Night_4": "Ever since I left my people, I've been searching for a new home... now I belong somewhere. That means everything to me. / 自从我离开我们一族之后，我一直在寻找一个新家……现在我有归属了。这对我来说就是一切。",
        "Neutral_2": "Do you think we could get in trouble for living together?$s / 你觉得我们同住会惹上麻烦吗？$s",
        "Rainy_Day_2": "Good morning, @. I went out early and found this for you. [305 308 203 795 397] / 早上好，@。我早起出门给你找到了这个。[305 308 203 795 397]#$e#I hope it's not too strange. / 希望这东西不会太奇怪。",
        "Outdoor_4": "Please go about your day, I'll just stay here and guard the house. / 你去忙着，我还是呆在这里看着房子吧。",
        "Indoor_Day_Krobus": "I wish I could help you on the farm, but I can't go out in the sun... / 我很希望能到农场上帮你，但是我没法呆在太阳底下……",
        "Neutral_8": "I'm going to clean the house all day! This is fun.$7 / 今天一天我都要做家务啦！这很有意思。$7",
        "Rainy_Day_3": "I wonder if the wizard knows about... this? I hope he can keep a secret.$s / 不知道法师是不是知道……这个？我希望他能保密。$s",
        "Rainy_Night_1": "If the other shadow people knew about our living arrangement, they would... 'punish' me.$s / 假如别的暗影人听到我们的居住方式，他们会……“惩罚”我的。$s#$e#Most of them despise humans, you know. / 要知道，他们大多看不起人类。",
        "spring_Krobus": "It's 'spring' now, isn't it? I can smell the peppery aroma of wild horseradish. / 是到“春天”了吧？我能闻到野山葵发出的辛辣香味了。",
        "fall_8": "I don't feel like doing anything today. / 我今天啥都不想干。",
        "TwoKids_3": "This house has been blessed with two children, now... Does that mean Yoba approves of our unconventional living arrangement? / 这间屋子现在被赐下两个孩子的祝福了……是不是说由巴认同了我们不同寻常的居住方式呢？",
        "Outdoor_0": "I'll stay out here for just a bit, but we've got to be careful... if anyone approaches I'll need to hide! / 我会在外面呆一会儿，但是还是得小心……万一有人来了我得藏起来！",
        "Rainy_Night_3": "I already had dinner, but it wasn't something you'd be able to eat... sorry. / 我已经吃过晚餐了，不过那些不是你能吃的东西……抱歉。",
        "fall_24": "If I showed up to the Spirit's Eve festival they'd put me in a cage...$s / 如果我去万灵节的话他们肯定会把我关到笼子里的……$s",
        "winter_28": "Thanks for letting me stay here, @. I'm looking forward to another great year!$h / 谢谢你能让我住在这里，@。希望明年能更好！$h",
        "Rainy_Day_4": "As much as I try to be civilized, I have the urge to be mischievous sometimes...$6 / 尽管我努力让自己保持礼貌，有时我还是有恶作剧的冲动……$6#$e#They say it's a condition of my people. / 他们说这是我种族的通病。",
        "summer_26": "... / ……",
        "summer_5": "... / ……",
        "Rainy_Night_5": "It's said that my people came here long ago, when a great catastrophe allowed spirits from the void to cross into the physical plane. / 听说很久以前发生了一场巨大的灾难，幽灵都能从虚空穿入物质世界。我们一族就是那个时候来到这里的。",
        "Rainy_Night_Krobus": "The sound of the rain reminds me of the sewers... it's comforting. / 雨点的声音让我想起了下水道……那里真的很舒适。#$e#The sewers were my refuge... I felt safe there. But don't worry... I feel the same way about my new home, too. / 下水道曾是我的避难所……我在那里有安全感。不过别担心……我在新家里也是同样的感受。",
        "Bad_4": "I think you'd be happier living with another human...$s / 我想你和别的人类一起生活也许会更开心的……$s",
        "Bad_5": "I've detected a change in your behavior... what does it mean? *groan*$s / 我感觉你的行为有些变化……是什么含义呢？（咕哝）$s",
        "Indoor_Night_3": "Sometimes I pause and think of all that I've learned about humans from you... / 有时我会停下来，回想我从你这里了解的人类的事情……#$b#I wish all my fellow shadow people could know this feeling. / 要是我们同族的暗影人都能理解这种感受该有多好。",
        "spring_5": "... / ……",
        "Indoor_Night_Krobus": "Hi, @. Welcome home. You look like you've been working hard out there!$h / 嗨，@。欢迎回家。看起来你干活挺辛苦的！$h",
        "Good_0": "We're making progress, and I feel really hopeful.$h / 我们有所进展，而且我感觉很有希望。$h",
        "Outdoor_3": "Wide open spaces make me nervous...$s / 在开阔的空间里我会紧张……$s",
        "spouseRoom_Krobus": "#$c .5#We're so physically different that it's a challenge to live together, isn't it? / #$c .5#我们身体的差别太大了，一起生活是不是也挺有挑战的？#$e#I hope the humidity here isn't bothersome to you. We both have to compromise in order to live together! / 但愿这里的湿度不会让你太心烦。要一起住，我们都要有所妥协！",
        "Indoor_Day_4": "On Fridays, I like to stay quiet out of respect for Yoba. I hope you don't mind. / 星期五的时候我喜欢保持安静，表示对由巴的尊敬。希望你不会介意。",
        "winter_19": "... / ……",
        "Neutral_7": "You're a strange one, to want to live with a creature like me. / 你还真是奇特呢，想和我这样的生物一起生活。",
        "Indoor_Night_2": "Sometimes I wonder if humans and shadow people could really ever co-exist... It's a lovely idea, but is it realistic?$s / 有时我会怀疑人类和暗影人是否真的能够共存……想法听起来很棒，但是这符合实际吗？$s#$e#I hope so... / 我希望如此……",
        "Good_1": "I feel a sensation in my body... is this... 'platonic love'?$l / 我身体里有一种感觉……这……是不是“柏拉图式爱情”？$l#$b#... Oh, wait... I'm just shedding my skin.$s / ……哦，等等……我只是在蜕皮。$s",
        "Bad_1": "*sigh*... Maybe I should've stayed with my own kind.$s / 唉……也许我就该跟我的同族一起呆着。$s",
        "Neutral_3": "It's so bright in here... I might close my eyes for a few hours.$s / 这里头好亮……我得闭上眼几个小时。$s",
        "fall_15": "Have you figured out what you're going to use for your grange display tomorrow? / 明天的农庄展览你要用什么确定好了吗？",
        "Neutral_6": "I'll tell you a secret... I don't actually sleep, I just lay there with my eyes closed... / 告诉你个秘密……实际上我是不睡觉的，我只是躺下来眯着……",
        "Good_2": "I've learned to overcome my bias against humans... but Dwarves still disgust me.$a / 我已经能克服我对人类的偏见了……不过我还是对矮人反感。$a",
        "Rainy_Day_0": "Do you like rainy days as much as I do, @? / 我很喜欢雨天，你呢，@？",
        "spring_1": "What's your plan for the new year, @? / 你的新年计划是什么，@？",
        "Bad_0": "...Do you still like me?$s / ……你还喜欢我吗？$s",
        "Outdoor_Krobus": "I'll wait here for a bit, and see if any bugs come my way. / 我会在这里等着，看看有没有虫子过来。#$e#I haven't had breakfast yet! / 我还没吃早饭呢！",
        "Bad_9": "I miss the sewers.$s / 我想念下水道了。$s",
        "spring_23": "You should go to the flower dance tomorrow! Don't worry about me. / 你明天去花舞节吧！别担心我。",
        "Outdoor_1": "It's rare that I can step outside! / 我能到外面来真是稀罕！",
        "winter_26": "... / ……",
        "Indoor_Day_3": "I'm considering spending my day all balled up and wedged in the corner... / 我在想要不要在角落里蜷起来呆一天……#$e#What? You mean you don't do that?$3 / 啥？你说你不会这么干？$3",
        "summer_12": "... / ……",
        "fall_Krobus": "It's been feeling a bit cooler lately, with a musty smell. You call this time of year 'fall', correct? / 最近感觉更凉快了，而且空气中有发霉的味道。这个时节你们是叫做“秋天”，没错吧？",
        "Indoor_Day_1": "I tried my best to make human food... [203 204 651 225] / 我尽力做了人类吃的菜……[203 204 651 225]#$e#You can eat it later, don't worry about it... / 你可以以后再吃，不用担心……",
        "Indoor_Day_0": "If I could come help you, I would... but I'll do my best to keep the house in order. / 要是我能过去帮你的话，我一定会的，可惜……不过我还是会尽力保持室内整洁。",
        "TwoKids_2": "I worry about the future of the children... But I trust that Yoba has a plan for them. / 我很担心孩子们的未来……不过我相信由巴已经有规划了。",
        "Neutral_1": "Do you think your Grandpa would approve of a monster living in his house? / 你觉得你爷爷会同意让怪物住在他的房子里吗？",
        "Rainy_Day_1": "We're different in so many ways... but that's alright. / 我们各方面都不太一样呢……不过这不要紧。",
        "spring_26": "... / ……",
        "winter_5": "... / ……",
        "Outdoor_2": "What a beautiful day!$h / 天气真好！$h",
        "fall_12": "... / ……",
        "OneKid_3": "I'm not sure how, but Yoba has blessed this house with a 'child'... / 由巴给这间屋子赐下了一个“孩子”的祝福，不过我不知道是怎么样……",
        "Neutral_4": "I can't go outside, I can only eat certain food, I need the temperature a certain way... I hope it's not too much of a bother to live with me, @.$s / 我没法外出，我很挑食，我对温度也有要求……但愿你跟我同住时没有感到很烦恼，@。$s",
        "spring_12": "... / ……",
        "Neutral_9": "I wonder if we'll live here our entire lives? Moving would probably be too dangerous for me. / 我们一生都会住在这里吗？搬家对我来说可能太危险了。",
        "Indoor_Night_0": "I cleaned all the bugs out of the house today... Sorry, I didn't save you any! *smack*$7 / 今天我把屋子里的虫子都除掉了……抱歉，一个都没给你留！（啪）$7",
        "fall_19": "... / ……",
        "TwoKids_0": "Don't worry... I already made %kid1 and %kid2 a void egg omelet. / 别担心……我已经给%kid1和%kid2做了虚空煎蛋卷。",
        "summer_Krobus": "You call this time of year 'summer', right? The warmth and humidity is nice, but I wish it wasn't so sunny. / 你们把一年的这个时候称作“夏天”，是吗？这湿热的天气不错，不过要是没那么晒就好了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/MarriageDialogueLeah",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "Bad_6": "We only have one short life to live... is this the best way to do it?$s / 我们的人生短暂……就这样子度过真的好吗？$s",
        "Indoor_Night_1": "The flow of time is so delicate... even the tiniest decision changes the future forever. / 时间的流逝真是微妙……即使是最小的决定也会永远地改变未来。",
        "Good_9": "Oh, I'm not bored... I'm just enjoying what we have here. / 哦，我并不无聊……我只是享受我们所拥有的一切。#$e#It's a simple life, but I like it.$h / 生活虽朴素，但我很喜欢。$h",
        "Bad_2": "Are you still happy with me?$s / 你和我在一起还幸福吗？$s",
        "fall_1": "I love fall for the mushroom hunting opportunities. It comes and goes pretty fast. / 我喜欢秋天采蘑菇。它们长得快也去得快。",
        "Good_4": "Mmm... You smell nice today. / 嗯……你今天的味道很好闻。",
        "Bad_8": "You've been so cold to me lately...$s / 最近你对我好冷淡……$s",
        "Neutral_0": "I hope you'll still like me when I'm old and gray. / 等到我白发苍苍，我希望你还会喜爱我。",
        "Good_5": "I was just admiring my wedding amulet... I'll cherish this treasure for the rest of my life.$l / 我刚刚在欣赏我的婚礼护身符呢……我余生都会珍惜这个宝贝。$l",
        "summer_9": "Sorry if I'm wet to the touch... I was sweating all night in the heat. / 如果我身上湿湿的那我很抱歉……今晚热得我全身冒汗。",
        "funReturn_Leah": "I had a nice, relaxing time today. How did your day go? / 今天我过得轻松愉快。你过得怎么样？",
        "summer_1": "Ah, summer... I can smell the spice berries already.$h / 啊，夏天……我已经能闻到浆果的芳香了。$h",
        "Indoor_Day_2": "Always remember to keep your eyes peeled for wild food! There's lots out there. / 记住留意寻找野生食物！这里有很多。",
        "Neutral_5": "Are we doing okay on money, @? / 家里是不是有些拮据，@？",
        "Indoor_Night_4": "I saw a wild rabbit today. I just wish I could pet one someday. They look so soft... / 今天我看到了一只野兔。我希望哪一天我能养一只。它们看起来很温和……",
        "Bad_3": "Did I do something wrong? You've been acting different lately.$s / 我做错什么了吗？你最近的反应不太一样。$s",
        "Rainy_Night_2": "It's going to be relaxing to fall asleep on a night like this...$l / 在这样的晚上睡觉很令人放松……$l",
        "Rainy_Night_0": "How was your day? Did you see any animals out there? / 今天过得怎么样？你在这里看到什么动物了吗？",
        "spring_15": "*sigh*... I guess it's time for the 'spring cleaning' again.$s / *唉* ……看来又到“春季大扫除”的时间了。$s",
        "patio_Leah": "Don't look too close, it's a work in progress. / 不要靠太近去看，它还只是一个半成品。",
        "Good_8": "Don't worry about me... I know you've got a lot of responsibilities outside of the house. I'm fine in here by myself!$l / 别担心我……我知道你在外面担负着许多责任。我自己一个人没事的！$l",
        "Good_3": "Wow, you look full of energy today!$l / 哇哦，你今天看起来精力充沛！$l^You look beautiful today.$l / 你今天看起来很美。$l",
        "Bad_7": "I used to be your sweetie... now you only seem to put up with me when I make a hot dinner.$s / 我曾经是你眼中的宝贝……但现在，只有做顿热腾腾的晚餐才能让你容忍我。$s",
        "Rainy_Night_4": "I'm glad you're home... It's a good night to get under the covers and stay warm. / 你回来真是太好了……今晚很适合躲在屋檐下取暖。",
        "fall_20": "Have you planned for winter at all? It's good to have a stockpile of hay. / 你安排好冬天的计划了吗？储藏干草很不错。",
        "Rainy_Day_2": "Good morning! I got up early and did some mushroom hunting. Here, take one.[281 404 420 257] / 早啊！我起得很早，然后采了些蘑菇。来，拿一个去吧。[281 404 420 257]#$e#Searching for mushrooms is like going on a treasure hunt. It's a lot of fun.$h / 寻找蘑菇就像是在寻找宝藏一样。很有趣。$h",
        "summer_2": "It's summer... that means the house is full of flies. / 夏天到了……估计要满房子苍蝇了。#$e#Don't worry, I'll take care of them. / 别担心，我会处理它们的。",
        "Neutral_2": "Don't you have anything to do today? / 你今天不是有事要做吗？",
        "Outdoor_4": "Don't overwork yourself, dear. / 亲爱的，别累着自己了。#$e#Make sure and take a break every now and then, or get something to eat.$h / 记得不时地休息一下，或者吃点东西。$h",
        "Neutral_8": "No matter how much I clean, the house keeps getting dirty again. / 不管我怎么打扫，房子还是会变脏。#$e#I guess farms can be kind of dirty. / 也许是农场本来就挺脏的吧。",
        "Rainy_Day_3": "It's days like this I'm really happy about my heavy-duty boots.$h / 在这样的天气，我很高兴我有一双结实的靴子。$h",
        "Rainy_Night_1": "I usually go for salad... but a wet night like this gives me cravings for hot soup.$h / 我常吃沙拉……但是像这样雨夜让我很想喝点儿热汤。$h",
        "funLeave_Leah": "I'm going to take a nature walk today. I need to get out of the house. / 我今天要散一下步。我要到房子外面去。",
        "TwoKids_3": "We've got a wonderful farm and a full family. Our new life has really turned out well, hasn't it? / 我们的农场生活很美好，并拥有一个完整的家庭。我们的新生活很棒，对吧？",
        "Outdoor_0": "The cool breeze feels nice. It reminds me of living by the river. / 凉爽的微风让人很舒服。这让我想起了住在河边的时光。",
        "Rainy_Night_3": "I made a little wood sculpture today, but it was so ugly I threw it into the fire.$u / 今天我刻了个小木雕，但是太丑了，所以我把它烧了。$u#$e#I think to become a great artist, you have to be critical of your own work. / 我认为要成为一个伟大的艺术家，必须批判对待对自己的作品。",
        "winter_28": "Hey, here's to another great year at %farm farm! Let's have some fun tonight! [348]$h / 嘿，%farm农场又度过了美好的一年！我们今晚庆祝一下吧。[348]$h#$e#Next year is going to be great, I can feel it. / 我有预感明年会更好。",
        "winter_1": "Winter's here, and that means crystal fruit is in season. It has such a unique flavor, don't you think? / 冬天了，这意味着会出现水晶果。它味道非常独特，你不觉得吗？",
        "Rainy_Day_4": "The trees have been begging for this rain... I'm happy for them. / 树林急需这场雨……我很高兴……",
        "fall_2": "I know harvest season is a busy time for you. I'll try and help out as much as I can. / 我知道在收获季你很忙。我会尽力帮助你的。",
        "Bad_4": "Do you ever wonder what else is out there?$s / 你有没有想过外面还有什么新事物？$s",
        "Bad_5": "You used to be romantic... what happened?$s / 你以前那么浪漫……到底怎么了？$s#$e#I know I'm not as young as I used to be... is that what you married me for?$a / 我知道自己没有以前那么年轻了……难道你和我结婚就是为了我当时的年轻貌美？$a",
        "Indoor_Night_3": "I never thought I'd receive a mermaid's pendant so soon after moving here! I'm happy about it, though.$l / 我从没想到过我搬来这里后这么快就能收到美人鱼吊坠！但是我很开心。$l",
        "Rainy_Night_Leah": "How was your day today, dear? Muddy? / 亲爱的，今天过得怎么样？身上没粘上泥吧？",
        "Good_0": "Living here, I feel like I'm on the summit of a great mountain. / 住在这里，我感觉就像像站在山顶一样。",
        "Outdoor_3": "Ah... that smell of fresh dirt. There's nothing quite like it.$h / 啊……新鲜泥土的芬芳。简直独一无二。$h#$e#You can just tell the air is clean here... it feels good in the lungs. / 这里的空气明显很干净……肺里感觉很好。",
        "Good_6": "Be careful out there! Sometimes I worry about you falling into a mine shaft. / 出去要小心啊！有时我总会担心你跌到矿井里。",
        "Indoor_Day_4": "Good morning, @! I made us some coffee.[395]$h / 早上好啊，@！我泡了些咖啡。[395]$h#$e#My morning just wouldn't be complete without a hot cup of coffee. / 没有一杯热咖啡，我的早上就是不完整的。",
        "winter_7": "I'm looking forward to carving ice sculptures tomorrow. I only get to do it once a year, but it's a lot of fun! / 我非常期待明天的冰雕。我每年只玩一次，但是很有趣！",
        "Neutral_7": "I don't really feel like doing anything today. / 今天我真的什么都不想做。",
        "Indoor_Night_2": "It's so much lovelier here at night than the garish glow of the city. / 这里的晚上比城市的霓虹更吸引人。#$e#Everything worked out perfectly for me. I'm very lucky. / 对我来说一切都很完美。我很幸运。",
        "Good_1": "Did I ever tell you... when you first moved here I had a dream that we'd be together someday. / 我有没有告诉过你……你第一次搬到这里的时候，我梦到过有一天我们会在一起。",
        "Bad_1": "*sigh*... Maybe we got married too young.$s / *唉* ……也许我们结婚太早了。$s",
        "Neutral_3": "If you go into town, make sure and say hi to everyone for me. / 要是你去镇子里，记得替我向大家打个招呼。",
        "Neutral_6": "I wonder what everyone in town is doing today? / 不知道镇里的朋友们今天会做些什么呢？",
        "Good_2": "Sometimes it's hard not to believe in destiny... the fact that I decided to move here, and that we found each other. / 有时候很难不相信命运……事实是我决定搬到这里，并找到了彼此。#$b#It could've gone entirely differently at any point. / 在任何一个点上生活可能都会变得完全不同。",
        "Rainy_Day_0": "I sometimes find inspiration in the most unlikely of places. / 有时候我会在最不可能的地方找到灵感。",
        "spring_1": "That was some way to ring in the new year last night...$l / 昨晚敲响新年的钟声的方式还真特别……$l",
        "Bad_0": "...Do you still love me?$s / ……你还爱我吗？$s",
        "Bad_9": "I wonder if I could've done better.$s / 也许我应该更努力些。$s",
        "Outdoor_1": "Hmm... I'm going to do some maintenance over here. I just get the urge to do some hammering now and then. / 嗯……我要维护一下这里。有时候我只是很想敲敲打打。",
        "Indoor_Day_3": "I was thinking... life's too short to eat bad food. Luckily, we live in one of the best regions for fresh greens and vegetables! / 我在想……生命短暂，不能吃不好的食物。幸运的是，我们住的地方就是新鲜蔬菜的最佳产地之一！#$e#Here, I made you a healthy salad. [196] / 来，我为你做了健康的沙拉。[196]#$e#I'm surprised you aren't sick of my salad yet! / 我很惊讶你竟然不讨厌我做的沙拉！",
        "spring_2": "So, what are we planting this season? / 话说，这个季度我们种些什么呢？",
        "Indoor_Day_1": "Good morning, @. I've planted these in a little pot out back... [16 18 20 22 90 259 396 402] / 早上好啊，@。我在外面的花盆里种了这些……[16 18 20 22 90 259 396 402]#$e#I grew that with great love and attention. Enjoy it. / 我花了很多心思来种它。好好享受吧。",
        "Indoor_Day_0": "This house is a lot nicer than my old cabin! I don't miss it. / 这房子比我旧旧的小木屋好多了！我不想念它。",
        "Neutral_1": "I wonder who lived here before us? / 我在想，在我们来之前，谁住在这里？",
        "Rainy_Day_1": "I used to find rain depressing when I lived in the city. But here in Stardew Valley it's beautiful. / 我曾住在城市的时候，发现雨天让人消沉。但是在星露谷，雨天很美。",
        "Outdoor_2": "It's going to be a special day, I can sense it. / 我能感觉到，今天会是很特别的一天。",
        "Good_7": "@? I just want to say that I appreciate all the hard work you do for our household.$h / @？我只是想说，我要感谢你为我们一家做出的全部努力。$h",
        "OneKid_3": "It's fun to be a parent. I want to make sure %kid1 grows up to have a love for the outdoors. / 为人父母很有趣。我要确保%kid1长大后喜欢户外生活。",
        "Neutral_4": "I'll do the laundry tomorrow morning before you get up... that way you won't have any down-time. / 明早你起来之前我会把衣服洗了……这样你就可以专心劳作了。",
        "Neutral_9": "I wonder if we'll live here our entire lives? / 不知道我们这辈子会不会一直住在这里？",
        "Indoor_Night_0": "Something about this time of night makes me thirsty. / 晚上这个时候让我觉得很渴。"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/MarriageDialogueMaru",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "Indoor_Night_1": "I saw a shooting star earlier. I like to pretend it's MARILDA stopping by to check on us.$h / 我之前看到过流星。我喜欢假装是玛丽尔达过来巡视我们。$h",
        "spring_22": "If my brother wasn't such a hermit I'd invite him over for dinner sometime. / 我有时想邀请我哥哥共进晚餐，可是他不愿出门。",
        "fall_1": "With every season, a new section of the night sky becomes prominent. It's fascinating to witness. / 在每个季节，夜空中都有一片新的部分变得愈发明显。见证这一幕令人陶醉。",
        "Good_4": "For a while there I was considering building a robotic ${husband^wife}$. But you're a lot more fun!$h / 我曾经考虑过造一个机器老${公^婆}$。但是你更有趣！$h",
        "Outdoor_3": "Don't worry, I won't mind if you track mud into the house. It's fun to get a little dirty now and then. / 别担心，如果你把泥巴带进房子我是不会介意的。偶尔弄脏一下也很有趣。",
        "winter_2": "So, what are your plans for maintaining our income this winter? / 那么，这个冬天你打算如何维持我们的收益呢？#$e#You could do some fishing or foraging... / 你可以钓鱼或去野外采集……#$e#If you do any mining, promise me you'll be careful. / 如果你打算采矿，答应我要多加小心。",
        "Neutral_0": "I hope you'd still like me even if I gained weight. / 我希望即使我长胖了你还是会喜欢我。",
        "Good_5": "I was just admiring my wedding amulet... The shell is flawless. This is a very rare specimen!$l / 我刚刚在欣赏我的婚礼护身符呢……这贝壳完美无瑕。这是很罕见的标本。$l",
        "Good_6": "Last night, I had a dream that I was looking through a gigantic telescope. I saw something moving in the %noun nebula. Kind of spooky. / 昨晚，我梦到我使用一架巨大的望远镜。我看见%noun星云里面有东西在移动。有点吓人。",
        "Indoor_Day_4": "How do you keep your hands so soft with all that farm work? / 你是怎么在干了那么多农活的情况下还让手保持柔软的？",
        "Indoor_Day_2": "Finally, you're up! I was getting so hungry... *rumble*$h / 你终于起床了！我好饿……*肚子咕咕叫*$h",
        "Indoor_Night_4": "I'm really starting to love this old house. It's so cozy at night. / 我真的开始爱上这老房子了。晚上很惬意。#$e#Mom's done a great job improving the place.$h / 妈妈把这里改进得很棒。$h",
        "winter_15": "The winters have been disturbingly mild lately. / 近来，冬天简直温和得令人不安。",
        "Rainy_Night_2": "Dad's been tracking the weather patterns for the last twenty years. / 爸爸追踪了过去二十年的天气规律。#$e#It's a little too early to tell, but the results have revealed some abnormal trends. / 现在说有点太早了，但是结果显示了一些反常趋势。",
        "winter_Maru": "I'm really looking forward to having rhubarb pie in the spring. Oh... that tang, that zest! / 春天我十分期待大黄派呢。噢……那气味，那味道！",
        "Indoor_Night_2": "I can't decide if I'm craving chocolate cake or ripe strawberries. Or maybe both...? / 我决定不了是想吃巧克力蛋糕还是熟草莓。或者都想……？#$e#Be honest... am I gaining weight?$s / 说实话……我是正在长胖吗？$s",
        "Good_1": "Now that we live together, it's hard to imagine being alone again. / 既然我们住在一起了，那就很难再想象一个人的生活了。",
        "funReturn_Maru": "Mom and Dad are doing just fine. Their routine is still the same, even with me gone. How was your day? / 妈妈和爸爸都很好。他们的日常生活还是那样，即使是在我走之后。今天过得怎么样？",
        "Rainy_Night_0": "Make sure you don't leave your tools out in the rain! You wouldn't want them to get all rusty. / 别让工具淋在雨里！要是它们生锈就不好办了。",
        "Good_2": "Taking a break? That's good! / 在休息吗？很好呀！",
        "Rainy_Day_0": "I wonder how Penny is doing? Maybe I'll give her a call later today. / 我很好奇潘妮怎么样了？也许等下我会打给她。",
        "Good_3": "There's a lot of strategy to planning and running a farm. It's more intellectually stimulating than I thought! / 规划和管理农场时需要考虑很多方面。这比我想的更加费脑！",
        "summer_20": "I wonder if my brother will ever have the courage to ask Abigail out? / 不知道我哥哥是否有勇气邀请阿比盖尔出去？",
        "Rainy_Night_4": "I made some dessert! Make sure to brush your teeth before bed, though. [232 234 223 220]$h / 我做了一些点心！但是在上床前记得刷牙。 [232 234 223 220]$h",
        "Rainy_Day_2": "Hey! I had trouble sleeping last night so I fiddled around in my workshop for a bit. Here, I made this for you. [688 369 338 325 287] / 嘿！我昨天有点失眠，所以我在我的工作间捣鼓了一会儿。看，这是我为你准备的。[688 369 338 325 287]#$e#I hope you can find some use for it. / 我希望你能用得上。",
        "spring_1": "It's wonderful to see all the plants and animals come back to life during the spring. / 春天看到万物复苏的感觉真棒。",
        "summer_2": "I like to catalogue the different insects I see in summer. / 我喜欢把夏天看到的不同昆虫分类。",
        "fall_Maru": "The farm life is great, but I'm glad I still work at the clinic... It's an important service for the community. / 农场生活太棒啦，但我很高兴我还在诊所工作……医疗服务对社区来说至关重要。",
        "Outdoor_4": "I never realized the amount of care and planning necessary to run a farm! It's a lot like working in the laboratory. / 我从来没意识到管理一个农场需要多少精力和规划！简直就像是实验室的工作。",
        "OneKid_0": "Have you spent any time with %kid1 today? Kids need playtime in order reach their full potential. / 你今天有花时间陪%kid1玩耍吗？孩子们需要游戏时间才能充分发挥潜力。",
        "Outdoor_1": "With a little planning, we could automate most of the farm work and just relax! / 只要稍稍规划一下，我们就可以让大部分农活儿自动进行，我们放松就行了！",
        "summer_Maru": "The evenings are so warm, it's really the best time of year for stargazing. Who knows what might up there? / 晚上好暖和，这真是一年中最适合观星的时期！谁知道这里会出现什么呢？",
        "spouseRoom_Maru": "#$c .5#I got up early to do a little stargazing. / #$c .5#今天我提早起来看了会星星。#$e#I hope you don't mind if I spend some time on my projects today, honey. / 甜心，我今天要去做我的项目，希望你不会介意。",
        "Indoor_Day_3": "One of the best things about living on the farm is waking up to a chorus of songbirds. / 生活在农场最棒的事情之一就是早上在鸟儿的歌声中醒来。",
        "Neutral_8": "I feel uninspired today.$s / 我今天没有灵感……$s",
        "spring_2": "So, what's your strategy for optimizing the farm this year? / 那么你今天完善农场的策略是什么？",
        "funLeave_Maru": "I think I'll visit my parents today. I haven't seen them in a while. / 我想我今天会去看看我的父母。我有一段时间没见过他们了。",
        "Rainy_Day_3": "The only thing I dislike about rain is the fact that I can't do any stargazing! / 我唯一不喜欢雨天的一点是我看不到星星！",
        "Rainy_Night_1": "Hi @. How was your day... soggy? / 嗨，@。这么潮湿……你今天过得怎么样？#$e#This weather gives me gadget ideas... maybe if I funnel the rainwater it could power a mill? / 这天气让我想到一些关于小玩意儿的点子……如果我把雨水集中起来，或许可以推动一个磨坊？",
        "fall_25": "Winter's just around the corner. We need to double check the heating system, turn off the valves, and check all the insulation in the house. / 冬天近在眼前。我们需要再次检查一下供暖系统，关掉水阀，查看房间所有的保温层。#$e#Don't worry, dear. I'll take care of it all. / 亲爱的，别担心。我会照料好一切的。",
        "Indoor_Day_1": "I found this in my scrap pile. Think you could find a use for it? [286 287 205 732] / 我在废料堆里找到了这个。你觉得能把它派上用场吗？ [286 287 205 732]",
        "fall_3": "Fall always reminds me of going out woodcutting with my mom... it might be that smell of freshly cut wood and sap. / 秋天总是让我想起和妈妈出去伐木的时候……可能是因为新伐木材和汁液的味道吧。",
        "TwoKids_3": "My own workshop, two wonderful kids, and a beautiful plot of land. Life is pretty good. / 我自己的工作间，两个很棒的孩子还有一方美丽的土地。生活真美好。",
        "Outdoor_0": "Ahh... the farm smells great, it reminds me of the mountains near my parent's house. / 啊……农场很好闻，让我想起我爸妈房子旁边的山脉。",
        "Rainy_Night_3": "Can we have spaghetti in bed tonight? / 今天我们可以在床上吃意大利面条吗？",
        "Indoor_Day_0": "Hmm? Sorry, sometimes I get so lost in thought that I don't even realize what I'm doing. / 嗯？抱歉，有时候我会沉浸在自己的思绪里，甚至没有意识到自己在干什么。",
        "Rainy_Day_4": "Do I hear a leak in the roof? I'll have to check it out. I know a thing or two about carpentry from watching my mother. / 我是听到屋顶在漏水吗？我要检查一下。我从看我妈妈干活学了一点木匠活儿。",
        "Rainy_Day_1": "I was just daydreaming... do you think MARILDA is okay? I hope she finds some place where she truly belongs... / 我只是在幻想……你觉得玛丽尔达还好吗？我希望她能找到她真正属于的地方……",
        "winter_5": "I hope Dad's doing okay... he can get depressed in winter, when there's less opportunity for field research. / 我希望我爸爸最近过得还好……因为出门的机会少，他在冬天的时候会抑郁。",
        "Outdoor_2": "It's going to be clear tonight... I wonder if the %noun constellation will be visible? / 今晚会是晴空……我在想是否可以看见%noun星座吗？",
        "OneKid_3": "I have high hopes for our child. I've been reading all the scientific data on the best ways to raise children. / 我对我们的孩子寄予厚望。我一直在看关于抚养小孩最佳方法的科学资料。",
        "Rainy_Night_5": "My day wasn't all that exciting... I stayed inside because of the weather. / 今天我过得平淡无常……因为天气原因我一直待在屋子里。#$e#It was relaxing, though. I kicked back with the latest 'Schematics Weekly'. / 但是我很放松。阅读最新一期的“每周图表”又让我心情好起来了。",
        "OneKid_1": "What do you think... will %kid1 grow up to be a farmer? Or an engineer? / 你觉得……%kid1将来会不会成为一名农夫呢？或者一名工程师？",
        "spring_Maru": "I'm feeling excited for a new year of farming, @!$h / 新的一年耕种开始了，我好兴奋啊，@！$h",
        "patio_Maru": "I'm not sure what this is, yet... but it's fun to turn the old wrench now and then. / 目前我还不能确定这是什么……但是不时转一下这个旧扳手还蛮有趣的。",
        "Indoor_Night_0": "Did you see the moon tonight? It always looks spectacular on the horizon. / 今晚你看到月光了吗？在地平线上月亮看起来很壮观。",
        "Indoor_Night_3": "You did good work today! You deserve to relax the rest of the evening. / 你今天干得不错！晚上的剩余时间你应该放松一下。"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/MarriageDialoguePenny",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "spring_8": "Spring is probably my favorite season. There's a certain freshness in the air that fills me with hope. / 春天大概是我最喜欢的季节。空气里面满是生气，让我充满了希望。",
        "Indoor_Night_1": "Hmm... skirt or pants tomorrow? Oh, who am I kidding... I always go with the skirt. / 嗯……明天是穿短裙还是裤子？噢，我骗谁呢……我一直都是穿短裙。",
        "winter_6": "The falling snow reminds me of grandma, rocking by the fire. I have this vivid memory of her shadow, flickering against the orange wood... That was long ago. / 飘落的雪让我想起我奶奶，坐在火旁的摇椅上。我印象最深的是她的影子在橙色的木头上忽隐忽现。那是很久以前的事了。",
        "summer_16": "*phew*... I need to eat more melon to combat this heat! / *呼*……我需要吃更多甜瓜消暑！",
        "fall_1": "Fall... It makes me think of colored paper and glue. Maybe I'm spending too much time with the children.$h / 秋天……让我想到彩色的纸和胶水。可能是我和孩子们一起太久了。$h",
        "Good_4": "This place is really starting to feel like home.$l / 这地方真的开始有家的感觉了。$l",
        "winter_3": "How will we stay afloat this winter? Oh, you don't have to tell me... I trust you to make the right decisions. / 这个冬天我们要怎么维持生计？噢，你不必告诉我……我相信你会做出正确的决定。",
        "Good_0": "@...I still can't believe we're married...$l / @……我还是不敢相信我们结婚了……$l",
        "Outdoor_3": "I just saw a songbird flying due west. In Stardew Valley that's a very good omen.$h / 我看到正西方有一只燕子在飞。在星露谷，这是很好的预兆。$h",
        "Good_6": "Be careful out there! Sometimes I worry that you aren't eating enough wholesome food. / 出去要小心啊！有时候我担心你没有吃足够的健康食物。",
        "Indoor_Day_4": "Was I shy when we first met? It's funny to think about, now that we've come so far.$h / 我们第一次见面的时候我很害羞吗？现在想想我们已经走过漫漫长路还真有趣。$h",
        "summer_1": "Summer may be searing hot, but the humidity feels great on the skin. / 夏天真热，但是这湿度让皮肤很舒服。",
        "Indoor_Day_2": "You know, I think I'll read a book today. I picked up something new from the library last time I was there. / 嗯，我想我今天会看书。上次在图书馆的时候，我学到了一些新东西。#$e#Gunther asked me to say hi. / 冈瑟让我代他向你问好。",
        "Indoor_Night_4": "Ready to tuck in? I made the bed and everything...$11 / 准备好钻进被窝了吗？我把床和其他的都准备好了……$11",
        "Rainy_Night_2": "I was just thinking about that night we met in the bathhouse.$l / 我只是在想我们在公共浴室相遇的那一晚。$l#$e#I'll never forget that night...$l / 我永远不会忘记那一晚……$l",
        "Indoor_Night_2": "We have it good here. We should always try and remember those less fortunate than us. / 我们在这里过得很好。我们应该一直努力并记住那些没我们幸运的人。#$e#I'm just very grateful for what we have. / 我只是很感激我们所拥有的东西。",
        "fall_5": "The smell of fall reminds me of the smell of books... weird, isn't it? / 秋天的味道让我想起书的味道……很奇怪，不是吗？",
        "Good_1": "I had dreams of marrying you for such a long time.$l / 我一直都梦想和你结婚。$l",
        "Rainy_Night_0": "How was your day, honey? I spent my afternoon reading a novel. / 亲爱的，今天过得怎么样？我一下午在读一本小说。",
        "spring_15": "Ah, the 'spring cleaning'... I'm actually going to enjoy this. / 啊，“春季大扫除”……其实我很享受这个。",
        "Good_2": "I knew you were the one from the moment you moved here...$l / 自从你搬到这里，我就知道你是我的命中注定……$l",
        "Rainy_Day_0": "On rainy days my thoughts always drift toward cinnamon and cookies. / 雨天我总是想着肉桂和饼干。",
        "Good_3": "Wow, you look really handsome today! Did you shave?$l / 哇哦，你今天看起来帅呆了！你刮胡子了吗？$l^Wow, you look beautiful today. Did you do something different with your hair?$l / 哇哦，你今天看起来美极了。你换了发型吗？$l",
        "Rainy_Night_4": "I felt like making a nice dinner. I hope you like it. [212 214 225 209 200]$h / 我做了美美的晚餐。希望你喜欢。 [212 214 225 209 200]$h",
        "Rainy_Day_2": "Hi, honey! I did some shopping this morning and got this for you.[186 180 770 535] / 嗨，甜心！今天早上我出去买东西了，并为你带了这个。[186 180 770 535]#$e#I thought you could really use one of those.$11 / 我觉得你一定用得上这个。$11",
        "spring_1": "We've got a long, warm year to look forward to. Let's make it a productive one. / 期望今年天气暖和。我们要在今年丰收。",
        "summer_2": "In summer, the ants become very active. I could watch them for hours... they have a pretty complex civilization from the looks of it! / 夏天，蚂蚁会变得活跃起来。我可以看它们好几个小时……从它们的外观来看，蚂蚁一定有复杂的文化。",
        "funReturn_Penny": "I had a nice time... It's good to stay in contact with everyone. Tell me about your day. / 我玩得很愉快……与大家保持联系感觉很好。说说今天过得怎么样啊。",
        "Outdoor_4": "Ahh... It feels great to be outside. I could spend all day right here, observing every little thing. / 啊……在外面感觉可真不错！我可以在这儿待一整天，观察每种小事物。",
        "OneKid_0": "Have you had any time to play with %kid1 today? Maybe a second child will make things better. / 你今天有花一点儿时间和小%kid1玩耍吗？也许再生一个小孩会更好些。",
        "funLeave_Penny": "I'm going to head into town today, just for fun. I'll be back in a while! / 我今天要去镇子里放松一下。我一会儿就回来！",
        "Outdoor_1": "Isn't this a perfect place to raise children? / 这难道不是抚育孩子的完美地方吗。#$e#I would've been so happy growing up on a farm. / 能在农场长大我简直再开心不过了。",
        "patio_Penny": "This is a lot more peaceful than my old spot in town. I'm very happy here. / 这比我在镇里的老地方更平静。我在这里很高兴。",
        "Indoor_Day_3": "I love to hear about all the artifacts you've found. Archaeology is fascinating! / 我喜欢听你讲找到的那些古物。考古让人着迷！#$e#To think... there may have been farmers at this very spot 10,000 years ago. / 想想看…… 10000 年前这个地方可能就有农夫了。",
        "Rainy_Day_3": "Hmm... maybe I should experiment with a new recipe. You liked the last recipe I made, didn't you, honey? / 嗯……也许我应该试验一下新配方。甜心，你喜欢我上次的那个配方，对吧？#$e#What was it called... 'Chili de @'? / 叫什么来着……“红辣椒@”？",
        "Rainy_Night_1": "I'm sure Mom's at the saloon right now... But I don't feel so bad about it anymore. It's out of my hands. / 我想我妈现在肯定在酒吧……但是我对这件事感觉没那么糟糕了。我无能无力了。",
        "Indoor_Day_1": "Good morning, @! I made you a hot breakfast.[195 210 211] / 早上好啊，@！我给你做了热腾腾的早餐！[195 210 211]#$e#It's important to me that you leave here with a full belly.$h / 你填满肚子再离开对我来说很重要。$h",
        "TwoKids_3": "A nice house, two wonderful kids, and a beautiful plot of land. We're so very fortunate. / 一栋漂亮的房子，两个可爱的孩子还有一方美丽的土地。我们真幸运。",
        "Outdoor_0": "I only ever dreamed of living in such a beautiful place, and now it's come true. / 我以前只是梦想能住在这样美丽的地方，现在美梦成真了。#$e#I was so miserable back home.$s / 我曾经在家的时候过得很悲惨。$s",
        "Rainy_Night_3": "The sound of rain used to bother me, when I lived in that old metal trailer. But it's quite soothing here. / 我住在那个老拖车里的时候，雨声曾困扰我。但在这里雨声却让人慰藉。",
        "Indoor_Day_0": "It's so peaceful here. I used to have the most horrific nightmares, but now I sleep like a baby. / 这里真宁静。我过去经常做最恐怖的噩梦，但是现在我睡得很香。",
        "TwoKids_2": "I've had this dream that %kid2 grew wings and flew into the night sky. What does it mean? / 我梦到%kid2长了翅膀，飞向夜空。这意味着什么？",
        "winter_1": "Winter's a good time to unwind a bit. You deserve it after the long year! / 冬天是放松的好时候。在漫长的一年后值得好好放松一下！",
        "Rainy_Day_4": "On days like this, I love to curl up with a good book. / 在这样的日子里，我喜欢窝起来读一本好书。",
        "fall_2": "Will you grow any giant pumpkins this year?$11 / 你今年会种巨型南瓜吗？$11",
        "Rainy_Day_1": "I wonder if Maru and Dr. Harvey will ever get together? I'm sure Harvey likes her... / 不知道玛鲁和哈维医生会不会在一起？我确定哈维喜欢她……#$e#I think Maru will have to make the first move, though.$h / 但是我觉得玛鲁可定会先踏出第一步。$h",
        "Outdoor_2": "Hi, honey! If I knew more about farm work I'd help you out more. Sorry! / 嗨，甜心！要是我多懂些耕种的知识，我一定会多帮帮你的。对不起！#$e#I'll be thinking of you.$h / 我会一直想着你的。$h",
        "OneKid_3": "I feel a lot older now that we have a child. Maybe it's just this new responsibility weighing on me. / 自从我们有了孩子后，我感觉自己老了很多。也许只是因为我承担了新的责任。#$e#It's not bad! I've wanted this for a long time.$11 / 这感觉还不错！我早就期待着养育孩子了。$11",
        "OneKid_1": "Little %kid1 is going to have such a great childhood here. / 小%kid1将在这里度过快乐的童年。",
        "Indoor_Night_0": "Good evening, honey. Did you accomplish everything you wanted to today? / 甜心，晚上好。你做完今天想要做的事了吗？#$e#If not, that's okay. We've got all the time in the world! / 如果没有，也没关系。我们有的是时间！",
        "TwoKids_0": "I already gave %kid1 and %kid2 their food. They're such hungry children! / 我已经给%kid1和%kid2喂过饭了。他们真是饿了！",
        "TwoKids_1": "We have to make sure and give %kid1 a lot of attention now that we have %kid2. We don't want any jealousy between them. / 有了%kid2后，我们要记得多关注些%kid1。我不想让他们嫉妒对方。",
        "Indoor_Night_3": "Mom's probably pretty lonely now that I'm gone. I just hope she doesn't visit the saloon more to make up for it. / 因为我离开了她身边，妈妈现在可能很孤独。我只是希望她不要太频繁的去酒吧来打发寂寞。#$e#You shouldn't feel bad! Mom has to solve her own problems.  / 你不用感到难过！妈妈必须解决她自己的问题。 "
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/MarriageDialogueSam",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "Indoor_Night_1": "My day? Oh... I can hardly remember. I didn't really do anything of note. Just relaxed and had a good time. / 我的一天？噢……我差点忘了。我还真没有做什么值得一提的事情。只是轻松地度过了一天。",
        "fall_1": "It seems like the whole valley's changed overnight... I guess fall's finally here. / 就像一夜之间整个星露谷都变了……我猜秋天来了。",
        "Good_4": "Baby, I was just gonna write you a song on the guitar. But now you're here and I feel relaxed. / 宝贝，我刚要为你写一首用吉他弹奏的歌。但是你在这里，我感觉很放松。#$e#I mainly feel like playing guitar when I'm lonely. / 我一般孤独的时候才想弹吉他。",
        "summer_10": "Have you thought about what you're going to put in the luau soup? / 你想好在宴会的汤里面放什么了吗？#$e#It might be funny to put something nasty. You know, to play a prank on the governor!$h / 放点儿恶心的东西应该很有趣。你知道的，跟州长开个玩笑！$h#$e#Sorry... / 抱歉……",
        "Outdoor_3": "Something in the air makes me feel positive... maybe it's the faint whiff of pizza from Gus' ovens. / 空气中的气息让我感觉很乐观……也许是格斯烤炉里披萨飘出来的香气。",
        "Good_5": "Baby, talk to me! I'm always interested to hear about your day. / 宝贝，跟我说说话。我很想听你今天过得怎么样。",
        "Good_6": "Be careful out there! I know you go into the caves sometimes... you could be eaten alive in there! / 出去要小心啊！我知道你有时候会去山洞……你可能会在那里被生吞活剥！",
        "Indoor_Day_4": "Um... Maybe I'll help out on the farm some other day. I feel lazy today.$s / 呃……也许未来某天我会在农场帮忙。我今天感觉很懒啊。$s#$e#You're not mad? / 你不会生气吧？",
        "winter_7": "Are we going to stop by the ice festival tomorrow? It might be fun to see everyone again... / 明天我们要顺便路过冰雪节吗？再次见到大家可能很有趣……",
        "summer_1": "The pollen count is a little lower in summer, so my nose is really happy.$h / 夏天花粉比较少，所以我的鼻子很舒服。$h",
        "Indoor_Day_2": "Hey. I know I joke around a lot, but I want you to know that I seriously love you...$l / 嘿。我知道我玩笑开过分了，但是我想让你知道我很认真的在爱你……$l",
        "Indoor_Night_4": "Ready to hit the hay? I actually made the bed for once... / 准备上床了吗？我偶尔铺了一次床……",
        "Rainy_Night_2": "Earlier, I listened to our live recording from that show we played. Remember that? Man, was that sloppy. / 早前，我在听我们之前那场表演的现场录音。还记得那场表演吗？天啊，真是烂透了。#$b#It made me a little nervous that you were there, I didn't want to mess up and have you think I was a loser!$10 / 因为有你在所以我有点儿紧张，我不想搞砸，让你觉得我是个失败者！$10",
        "Indoor_Night_2": "Hey, sorry I didn't make the bed. You know I'm sloppy... that's why you like me, right?$h / 嘿，抱歉我没有铺床。你知道我很邋遢……所以你才喜欢我，对吧？$h",
        "Good_1": "Do you ever think of that night we snuck into my room? I do, often...$l / 你会回想起我们溜进我房间的那晚吗？我常常想起……$l",
        "Rainy_Night_0": "Hey, how was your day? I just lay around and read comics most of the day... it was great.$h / 嘿，你今天过得怎么样？我今天大部分时间都躺在屋里看漫画……真爽。$h",
        "fall_15": "Hey, tomorrow's the fair. I need to get my old slingshot wrist back in shape... / 嘿，明天就是集市了。我得把生疏的弹弓技巧练回来……",
        "fall_26": "I wonder if Mom will let Vincent enter the haunted maze this year. Probably not...$h / 我想知道今年妈妈是否会让文森特去鬼屋。可能不会……$h#$e#Poor kid. He's gonna have to grow up some day... / 可怜的孩子。他总有一天要长大的……",
        "Good_2": "You know, I think I had a feeling we'd be together from the very beginning. There's just something special between us.$l / 你知道吗，从一开始我就感觉我们会在一起。我们之间有一种特别的情愫。$l",
        "Rainy_Day_0": "Might be a good day to sit back and jam on the guitar... / 今天可能适合休息一下，弹一弹吉他……#$e#Hey, you can relax too if you want. / 嘿，如果你想的话也可以放松一下。",
        "Good_3": "Wow, you look really handsome today! Did you do something with your hair?$l / 哇哦，你今天看起来帅呆了！你换了发型吗？$l^Wow, you look stunning today. Did you do something new with your hair?$l / 哇哦，你今天看起来美极了。你换了发型吗？$l",
        "patio_Sam": "*Sigh*... I'm never gonna land this trick...$s / *唉*……我永远不会用这一招……$s",
        "Rainy_Night_4": "Hey, I tossed a couple frozen pizzas into the oven. Here's yours. [206]$h / 嘿，我在烤箱里烤了几片冷披萨。这是你的份。 [206]$h",
        "Rainy_Day_2": "Hey, I found one of these rolling around in the back of a drawer. [90 88 86 535] / 嘿，我在抽屉里面找到了这个。[90 88 86 535]#$e#I thought you might be able to use it. / 我想你也许用得上它。",
        "spring_1": "Ub... spring... my doze... allergies.$s / 呃……春天……我的鼻子……过敏。$s",
        "Outdoor_4": "Wow... you look great today, and the specks of mud just add some extra charm.$l / 哇哦……你今天看起来很棒，泥土又增加了额外的魅力。$l",
        "OneKid_0": "I'll change %kid1's diaper... don't worry about it. You've got enough on your plate. / 我会给%kid1换尿布……别担心。你要忙的事情已经够多了。",
        "funReturn_Sam": "Seeing family is nice, but it's also kind of depressing in a weird way. Like... our lives are totally separate now, and everything feels more formal than it used to.$7 / 回家探望是件好事，但不知怎的我会觉得有点压抑。就像……我们的生活完全分开，一切都比以前更加拘谨。$7",
        "spring_23": "Oh... tomorrow's the flower dance, isn't it? I thought I could get out of it now that we're married. / 噢……明天是花舞节，不是吗？我以为我们结婚了就能摆脱它了。#$e#Whatever. I guess it's funny in a weird way. / 算了。我觉得它有一种奇怪的乐趣。",
        "Outdoor_1": "I always keep an eye on the wide blue sky... you never know when a UFO might go by. / 我一直盯着广阔的蓝天……你永远不会知道 UFO 会什么时候经过。",
        "Indoor_Day_3": "Do you have big plans for the day? / 你今天有什么打算？#$e#Oh, not me... I usually decide what to do a few moments beforehand... / 哦，我没有……我通常在开始前几分钟才决定做什么……",
        "summer_27": "Summer's great, but I'm ready for the fall now. / 夏天很棒，但是现在我准备好迎接秋天了。#$e#Should we watch the jellyfish tomorrow night? It's always kind of fun. / 明晚我们要去看水母吗？那很有趣。",
        "funLeave_Sam": "I'm gonna visit the family today, okay? I'll be home in the evening. / 今天我要回家看看，好吗？晚上我会回来。",
        "Rainy_Day_3": "Aw, man. These cloudy days are kind of a drag...$7 / 噢，阴天真是让人无精打采……$7",
        "Rainy_Night_1": "It was a pretty low-key day for me... colas, frozen pizza, a few hours noodling around on the guitar. I feel relaxed. / 对我来说今天真是低调的一天……可乐、冷披萨、即兴弹几小时的吉他。我感觉很放松。",
        "Indoor_Day_1": "Hey, I made you some instant pancakes. Enjoy. [211]$h / 生活变化无常。好好享受吧。[211]$h#$e#What? I never learned to cook... mom always did that. / 什么？我从没学过烹饪……一直都是妈妈在做饭。",
        "TwoKids_3": "I never thought I'd become such a family man, but I'm really satisfied with what we've built here. Life is going great.$h / 我从没想过我会成为一个居家男人，但是我对我们在这里构筑的一切都很满意。生活很美好。$h",
        "Outdoor_0": "Maybe I should get some off-road wheels for my skateboard. Mayor Lewis can't touch me out here.$h / 也许我应该为我的滑板装几个越野轮子。在这里市长刘易斯管不到我。$h",
        "Rainy_Night_3": "I hope Vincent's not too lonely now that I'm gone... I kinda felt responsible for the little guy.$s / 我希望文森特不会因为我不在了而感到太孤独……我觉得我要对他负责。$s#$e#But, life's all about change... right? Kids need to learn that, eventually... Or else adulthood will destroy them.$7 / 但是，生活变化无常……对吧？孩子们最终要学到这一点……不然成人的世界会击垮他们的。$7",
        "Indoor_Day_0": "Phew... I'll tell you one thing I don't miss about my old life... working at JojaMart. / 呼……我从前的生活中有一件事我丝毫不怀念……那就是在 Joja 超市的工作。",
        "TwoKids_2": "It's fun to see the babies playing with each other. I think they're going to be very close. / 看到孩子们玩在一起很有趣。我想他们会很亲密……",
        "winter_28": "We had a great year, @... it's kind of sad that it's over. / 我们度过了美好的一年，@……一年过完了还真是有点伤感。#$e#We'll just have to make next year even better!$h / 我们要让明年更好！$h",
        "winter_1": "The cold air makes my hair gel freeze. It's not very pleasant.$s / 冷空气让我的发胶凝固了。感觉不是很舒服。$s",
        "Rainy_Day_4": "How'd you sleep? The sound of rain really makes me zonk. / 你睡得怎么样？雨声让我睡得很沉。",
        "Rainy_Day_1": "Do you think Sebastian and Abigail will ever hook up? / 你觉得塞巴斯蒂安和阿比盖尔会在一起吗？#$e#Heh... now that I'm married I'm trying to get everyone else married too. / 哈哈……我现在结婚了，所以我也想让其他人步入婚姻。",
        "Outdoor_2": "Hi, @! If I knew more about farm work I'd help you out more. Sorry! / 嗨，@！要是我多懂些耕种的知识，我一定会多帮帮你的。对不起！#$e#I'll try and help you with encouraging thoughts.$h / 我会努力鼓励你的。$h",
        "OneKid_3": "I think we should have another kid. Why stop now? / 我想我们应该再生一个。为什么不呢？",
        "OneKid_1": "It's weird, but I really like being a father!$h / 这很奇怪，但我真享受作为一名父亲！$h",
        "spring_12": "Are you excited for tomorrow's festival? It'll be cool to see Sebastian again. / 你对明天的节日感到兴奋吗？能再见到塞巴斯蒂安太棒啦。",
        "Indoor_Night_0": "Hey, you look tired. Let me help you relax tonight, okay? Maybe I'll give you a massage later. / 嘿，你看起来很累。让我今晚帮你放松好吗？也许等下我会给你按个摩。",
        "TwoKids_0": "I woke up early, fed the kids and changed their diapers! We're all set. You can just focus on raking in that sweet money.$h / 我醒得很早，喂了孩子并换了尿布！我们都准备好了。你只要好好赚钱就行了。$h#$e#I'm just kidding... I didn't marry you for the money. / 我开玩笑的……我不是为了钱才和你结婚。",
        "TwoKids_1": "We have to make sure and give %kid1 a lot of attention now that we have %kid2. We don't want any jealousy between them. / 有了%kid2后，我们要记得多关注些%kid1。我不想让他们嫉妒对方。",
        "Indoor_Night_3": "The only thing I miss about living at home is Mom's fish casserole / 我只想念住在家里时妈妈做的砂锅鱼。"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/MarriageDialogueSebastian",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "Bad_6": "What do you want? You sound like my step-dad. Go away.$a / 您想怎样？你怎么跟我继父一个调调。快走开。$a",
        "Indoor_Night_1": "Maybe I drank too much coffee... I don't feel very tired. / 也许我喝太多咖啡了……我并没感到很累。#$e#I'm still trying to adjust to the farm schedule. I used to stay up until 5am and sleep in until 2pm, sometimes.$h / 我还在试着适应农场的生活方式。我过去偶尔熬夜到凌晨 5 点，然后睡到下午 2 点才起来。$h",
        "funLeave_Sebastian": "I'm going to take a walk today. I need some time to myself. I'll see you in the evening. / 我今天要散一下步。我需要一点属于自己的时间。晚上见。",
        "Good_9": "I don't really need friends. You're the only person I need in my life. Is that weird? / 我真的不需要朋友。你是我生命中唯一需要的人。是不是很奇怪？#$e#I guess I'm not like most people. / 我猜我跟大部分人不一样。",
        "fall_1": "It seems like the whole valley's changed overnight... I guess fall's finally here. / 就像一夜之间整个星露谷都变了……我猜秋天来了。",
        "Good_4": "You don't ever have to worry about me. I like to spend a lot of time alone. / 你不用担心我。很多时候我喜欢一个人。",
        "summer_10": "Have you thought about what you're going to put in the luau soup? / 你想好在宴会的汤里面放什么了吗？#$e#I have no idea what's good... you're the chef!$7 / 我不知道放什么好……你才是厨师！$7",
        "Bad_8": "I started smoking again... I've just been really stressed out lately.$s / 我又开始吸烟了……最近我压力重重。$s",
        "Neutral_0": "When I take walks I do my best to avoid everyone. I hate being pressured into small talk. / 我散步的时候尽可能避开每一个人。我不喜欢被迫跟别人寒暄。",
        "Good_5": "Sometimes I feel so angry... but when you show up I always start to calm down.$7 / 有时候我很生气……但是看到你之后我就会开始冷静下来。$7#$e#Maybe I'll mellow out with age. / 也许随着年龄增长，我会放松心态。",
        "summer_1": "Summer's here... I need to start slathering the sunscreen pretty thick if I want to maintain my pale complexion... / 夏天来了……如果我想让皮肤一直这么白，就要涂很厚的防晒霜……",
        "Indoor_Day_2": "I couldn't sleep last night so I went for a night ride on the motorcycle. / 昨晚我失眠了，所以我晚上出去骑摩托车了。#$e#I need to stay independent, even though we're married. That's just how I am. I still love you, though.$7 / 我要保持独立，即使我们结婚了。我就是这样。但我仍然爱你。$7",
        "Neutral_5": "Are we doing okay on money? I don't want to have to sell my laptop... / 家里是不是有些拮据？我不想卖掉我的笔记本电脑……",
        "Indoor_Night_4": "I often felt unappreciated back home... but here I feel like I really belong. Thanks for making me feel welcome, @.$l / 在家里我经常感觉被忽略……但是我感觉自己是真正属于这里。谢谢你让我觉得宾至如归，@。$l",
        "Rainy_Night_2": "Sorry, I didn't make any dinner. We might have a frozen pizza in the fridge or something. / 抱歉，我没做晚饭。我们可以吃点冰箱里的冷披萨或者别的。#$e#I dunno, my mind was elsewhere. It's hard to remember to do chores... / 我不知道，我在想别的。我经常会忘记做家务……",
        "Rainy_Night_0": "I'm trying my best to quit smoking now that we're married... I don't wanna die on you. It's a bad habit. / 既然我们结婚了，现在我在尽最大努力戒烟……我不想比你先去世。这是个坏习惯。#$e#I want to have a future together.$l / 我想和你共创未来。$l",
        "fall_26": "I'm excited for the Spirit's Eve tomorrow. I wonder what horrors we'll find there.$h / 明天的万灵节真让我感到兴奋。不知道会看到什么恐怖的东西。$h",
        "Good_8": "I don't really feel like doing work today. Maybe I'll see what's on TV. / 我今天没什么工作的心情。也许我应该看电视。",
        "Good_3": "I don't often show it, but I'm really happy that I'm your husband. Marrying you was the best decision I ever made.$l / 我不经常表达，但是能成为你的丈夫我很幸福。娶你是我做过的最好的决定。$l",
        "Bad_7": "This place is starting to feel like a tomb.$s / 这地方感觉像墓地。$s",
        "Rainy_Night_4": "Maybe a witch will visit us tonight? Hah.. if only life was that interesting... / 或许今晚会有一位女巫前来拜访？哈……如果生活有那么有趣就好了……",
        "Neutral_2": "Why don't you tell me about your day when we're in bed tonight? I'm kind of busy right now... / 等我们今晚躺在床上的时候再给我讲讲你的一天吧？我现在有点忙……",
        "Rainy_Day_2": "Hey. I couldn't sleep last night so I took a walk to the caves. I found this... want it?[575 769 767 84 66 78] / 嘿。昨晚我睡不着，所以我去山洞走了走。我找到了这个，想要吗？[575 769 767 84 66 78]#$e#I just have trouble sleeping sometimes, it has nothing to do with you. I love you.$7 / 我只是偶尔会失眠，这与你无关。我爱你。$7",
        "Outdoor_4": "We should raise more slimes... In big quantities they can be pretty profitable. And they're so easy to raise. / 我们应该多养点史莱姆……大量养殖利润相当可观。它们很好养。#$e#Also, different colored slimes produce different items. I dunno, I think it'd be kind of a fun hobby for us. / 并且，不同颜色的史莱姆可以产出不同的物品。我不知道，我觉得那是一种有趣的爱好。",
        "OneKid_0": "I'm still getting used to being a father. Don't worry, I'll take good care of %kid1! It's just... something new. / 我还在努力适应当一名父亲。别担心，我会好好照顾%kid1的！只是……我还不太习惯。",
        "Neutral_8": "House-cleaning isn't fun, but when I listen to music, it goes by pretty fast. / 打扫房子没什么意思，但是当我边听音乐边打扫时，就会过得很快。",
        "summer_27": "The weather's starting to cool off. It feels great. / 天气开始转凉了。这感觉棒极了。#$e#Should we go to the festival tomorrow night? It's actually a tradition I kind of enjoy.$7 / 明晚我们要不要去参加节日？实际上我很喜欢这个传统。$7",
        "Rainy_Day_3": "Seems like a pretty good day to just lay around, maybe read a book or something... what do you think? / 今天似乎很适合躺着，或许看书或者做点别的……你觉得呢？",
        "Rainy_Night_1": "I did some work on the laptop today. I was actually brainstorming some ideas for a game I want to make. / 我今天用笔记本电脑完成了些工作。实际上我想出了一些我想做的游戏的点子。#$e#With your farming income, I can afford to do what I want with my life. It's pretty amazing. Thank you.$h / 靠着你的农场收入，我可以实现自己的人生理想。太棒啦。谢谢。$h",
        "TwoKids_3": "We've come a long way, @. Look at our family. To be honest, I never really thought I'd end up in this situation. / 我们走过了漫长的路，@。看看我们的家庭。说实话，我从未料到我会有今天这样的处境。#$e#Now that I'm here, I like it...$l / 既来之，则安之……$l",
        "Outdoor_0": "I feel like I want to do something today... but I'm not sure what. Do you ever have that problem, @? / 我今天想做点什么……但是我不确定。你有没有这么觉得过呢，@？",
        "Rainy_Night_3": "How was your day? Did you slay any monsters?$h / 今天过得怎么样？你有没有杀死什么怪物？$h#$e#It feels good to take out your aggression now and then, doesn't it? / 不时发泄一下的感觉也很好，不是吗？",
        "winter_28": "It's been a great year, @. We should celebrate a little. [346]$h / 今年过得真棒，@。我们应该稍稍庆祝一下。[346]$h#$e#I'm sure next year will be even better.$7 / 我相信明年会更好。$7",
        "winter_1": "What are your plans this winter? I know it's more of a laid-back time for you. / 今年冬天你有什么计划？我知道你在冬天过得比较轻松。",
        "Rainy_Day_4": "Hey, another rainy day... perfect. / 嘿，又是雨天……太好了。#$e#You look cold... here, come closer.$l / 你看起来很冷……来，靠近点儿。$l",
        "Bad_5": "Look, I just want to be alone. Why don't you go outside and do your own thing for a while? / 拜托，我只想自己一个人呆着。你为什么不去外面做你自己的事情？",
        "Indoor_Night_3": "I spotted a bat out the window earlier. It's kind of hard to see, but if you stay focused you can often catch them flittering about. They're out there. / 之前我在窗户外面看到了一只蝙蝠。它们很难看到，但是如果你集中注意力，可以经常看到它们一掠而过。它们就在那里。",
        "patio_Sebastian": "Need something? I'll just be over here working on my bike for a while. / 有事吗？我就在这摆弄一会我的摩托车。",
        "Good_0": "Hey. Look at me. Never forget that I love you... you're everything to me.$l / 嘿。看着我。别忘了我爱着你……你是我的一切。$l#$b#Now go make us some money.$h / 现在去为我们挣些钱吧。$h",
        "Outdoor_3": "I don't want to get soft now that I'm a married guy. Maybe I should start eating more hot pepper and working out? / 我不想因为结婚而变得柔弱。也许我该开始多吃点红辣椒，并锻炼身体？#$e#Just an idea...$h / 只是想想而已……$h",
        "Good_6": "I know you're tough, but I still worry about you, sometimes. Don't ever go monster hunting without a life elixir and some sturdy boots, okay? / 我知道你很坚强，但有时候我还是会担心你。去狩猎怪物的时候一定要记得带上生命药水和耐用的靴子，好吗？",
        "Indoor_Day_4": "Living here with you is teaching me to come out of my shell a little bit. I think it's good for me.$7 / 和你住在这里让我学会了走出自己的堡垒。我觉得这样对我很好。$7",
        "winter_7": "Are you going to enter the fishing contest tomorrow? / 你要参加今年的钓鱼大赛吗？",
        "Indoor_Night_2": "It's really cool to have our own place. I can do whatever I feel like and not have people nagging at me all the time. / 拥有我们自己的小窝感觉真好。我想做什么就做什么，不会一直受人唠叨。#$e#I'm sure Maru's happy that I'm gone. / 我走了玛鲁肯定很高兴。",
        "Good_1": "Hey... come here. You look great today.$l / 嘿……过来！你今天看起来很棒。$l",
        "Neutral_3": "Are you going into town today? Why, what are you up to? / 你今天会去镇子里吗？为什么，你有什么事？",
        "fall_15": "The Stardew Valley Fair is a little crowded for my tastes... but I'll just hang out with Sam. It'll be good to catch up with him. / 星露谷集市对我来说有点儿挤……但我只是和山姆闲逛。跟他交流一番应该挺不错。#$e#You should play some carnival games, though! Don't worry about me.$7 / 但你也应该玩一玩摊位游戏！不要担心我。$7",
        "Neutral_6": "If you need to go see your friends in town, go ahead. I like being alone, anyways. / 如果你要去镇子见你的朋友，那就去吧。不管怎样，我喜欢一个人。",
        "Good_2": "You always look great, even after slopping around in the yard all day.$l / 你一直看起来很棒，即使在院子里弄得满身都是泥之后。$l",
        "Rainy_Day_0": "Finally... some heavy rain. I get bored of sunny weather easily. / 终于……下大雨了。我很容易对晴天感到厌烦。",
        "spring_1": "Oohh... my head. Happy new year...$h / 噢……我的头。新年快乐……$h",
        "spring_23": "Oh... tomorrow's the flower dance, isn't it? Do we have to go? / 噢……明天是花舞节，不是吗？我们必须得去吗？#$e#I hate wearing that ridiculous tight jumpsuit. Why does Lewis make us do this?$s / 我讨厌穿着可笑又紧绷的连身衣。为什么刘易斯让我们这样做？$s",
        "Outdoor_1": "Hmm... sometimes I have to force myself to stay outside for health. / 嗯……为了健康，有时候我强迫自己待在外面。#$e#I dunno what it is, but I like being indoors. Maybe I'm just so used to my dark basement. / 我不知道这是什么感觉，但是我喜欢待在室内。也许我太习惯我昏暗的地下室了。",
        "Indoor_Day_3": "Hey. How'd you sleep last night? I heard you mumbling. / 嘿。你昨晚睡得怎样？我听到你说梦话了。#$e#You seemed scared, but I have to admit... it was kind of cute.$l / 你似乎被吓到了，但是我必须承认……那很可爱。$l",
        "Indoor_Day_1": "Hey... want some coffee?[395]$7 / 嘿……想来点咖啡吗？[395]$7#$e#I needed some... woke up early from a nightmare and I just couldn't fall back asleep. / 我想要点……之前从噩梦中醒来，我现在再也睡不着了。",
        "Indoor_Day_0": "The older I get, the less I'm drawn to the city. It had a certain mystique to it, once. But it turns out that was just a romantic fantasy. / 随着年纪越来越大，我就越不留恋城市了。城市曾经有某种神秘的魅力。但事实证明那只是一种浪漫的幻想。#$e#The city's so busy, so full of people... I don't belong there. I'm a loner. / 城市太繁忙，到处都是人……我不属于那里。我是个喜欢孤独的人。",
        "TwoKids_2": "I've had this recurring dream that %kid2 is wearing a shadow shaman costume and sitting on a glowing pumpkin. Weird, huh? / 我一直梦到%kid2穿着暗影萨满的衣服，坐在发光的南瓜上。很奇怪，对吧？",
        "Rainy_Day_1": "Hey. I was just thinking about my old room in the basement. I felt comfortable there, but this is a lot more interesting. And I don't miss the smell... / 嘿。我只是在想我在地下室的旧房间。我在那里感觉很舒服，但是这里更有趣些。而且我不喜欢那味道……#$e#I felt kind of embarrassed living in my mom's house for so long. / 住在我妈房子里这么久我觉得有点儿尴尬。",
        "Outdoor_2": "I'll just watch you from here.$h / 我会从这里看着你。$h#$e#I enjoy watching you. / 我喜欢看着你。",
        "OneKid_3": "Have you smelled %kid1? Maybe it's time for a bath... / 你闻到%kid1身上的味道了吗？也许该洗澡了……",
        "Neutral_4": "I guess I can do the laundry today... You probably have your hands full with running the farm. / 我向我今天可以洗衣服……你可能手上全是管理农场的事。",
        "OneKid_1": "Maybe when %kid1 is a little older, I'll get a sidecar for the bike and we can all go for a ride.$h / 也许等%kid1再长大点儿，我会给摩托装一个边车，然后我们就可以一起去兜风了。$h",
        "spring_12": "Are you excited for tomorrow's festival? It'll be good to see Sam again. / 明天的节日有没有让你感到兴奋？能再见到山姆真是太棒啦。",
        "Indoor_Night_0": "Hey. I just hung out around the house, today. Nothing interesting... / 嘿。今天我在房子周围闲逛了一下。没什么有意思的……#$e#... / ……#$e#The view from our house is perfect. You can see the sun setting over Pelican Town from the front porch. / 从我们的房子看过去，风景太美了。在前廊可以看到鹈鹕镇的日落。",
        "funReturn_Sebastian": "My day was fine, nothing much to tell you about. Why don't you tell me about yours? / 我过得很好，没什么好跟你说的。为何不跟我说说你今天过得如何？",
        "TwoKids_0": "Don't worry, I already fed the kids... %kid2 spilled the chocolate milk all over my shirt again. / 别担心，我已经喂过孩子了……%kid2又把巧克力牛奶洒到我衬衫上了。",
        "TwoKids_1": "I hope %kid1 and %kid2 are nice to each other. Maru and I always fought as kids. / 我希望%kid1和%kid2能相处地很好。我和玛鲁总是像孩子一样打架。#$e#If I think back on it, it was mostly my fault... / 现在回想起来，大部分时候都是我的错……"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Characters/Dialogue/MarriageDialogueShane",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "Bad_6": "What do you want? You sound like Marnie on one of her bad days. Go away.$a / 你想干嘛？你听起来就像心情很坏的玛尼。走开。$a",
        "Indoor_Night_1": "If... If only... ah, I was just thinking back on the glory days, when I played gridball on the varsity team.$6 / 要是……要是那时……啊，我只是在回忆当年在校队打格球的辉煌岁月。$6#$b#Now I'm old and weak, though... / 不过现在我又老又弱了……",
        "Good_9": "Huh... You're wondering why I have this goofy grin on my face? You really have a short memory span, don't you? *blush*$h / 嗯……你想知道我为什么在傻笑吗？你的记性真得不太好啊，不是吗？*脸红*$h",
        "fall_1": "Hmm... I might have to buy a few cases of pumpkin ale to celebrate the season...$6 / 嗯……我可能需要买一些南瓜啤酒来庆祝这个季节……$6",
        "Good_4": "Hey, if I ever seem cranky, just ignore it. I get in weird moods sometimes, but it's not about you... okay? / 嘿，如果我表现得很暴躁，无视我就好。有时我的情绪会很奇怪，但不是针对你……好吗？",
        "summer_10": "I might fast until the luau tomorrow. I need the ol' bag to be empty so I can fill it with piping hot soup.$h / 直到明天的夏威夷式宴会为止我应该禁食。我需要放空自己的肚子，这样才好痛饮滚烫的汤。$h",
        "funReturn_Shane": "Sorry if I'm sweaty... That was quite a walk... Buh, I'm out of shape.$6 / 抱歉我满身都是汗……我跑了好远……哎，我太胖了。$6",
        "Bad_8": "Yeah... *hic* ... Sure, honey. Whatever you say... *hic* / 是的……*嗝*……当然，亲爱的。随你怎么说……*嗝*",
        "Neutral_0": "Oh, do you need something from me? Sorry, I'm kind of busy at the moment. / 噢，你有事要找我吗？不好意思，我这会儿有点忙。",
        "Good_5": "Ah... life on the farm sure beats working at Joja. That place was disgusting.$h / 啊……在农场生活肯定比在 Joja 工作强。那个地方很恶心。$h#$e#You think it was depressing out front? Kid, you should've seen the back room... / 你认为在前面很沮丧吗？孩子，你应该看看后面的房间……",
        "summer_1": "I like seeing all the tropical plants this time of year. The valley gets so lush. / 我喜欢在每年的这个时候看到那些热带植物。山谷变得郁郁葱葱。",
        "Indoor_Day_2": "Do me a favor... when I pass away, use my dust to fertilize some corn for the hens. / 答应我一件事……等我去世以后，用我的骨灰给玉米施肥来喂母鸡吧。",
        "Neutral_5": "Are we doing okay on money? I don't want to have to go back to work at Joja. / 我们赚的钱多吗？我不想被迫回到 Joja 商场工作。",
        "Indoor_Night_4": "I spent all day watching TV and now my legs feel like soft dough. Guess I'll have to take it easy until tomorrow. / 我一整天都在看电视，现在我的腿感觉像柔软的面团。我想我得放轻松到明天。",
        "Rainy_Night_2": "I guess... if I had some pants I might've gone outside today... but, nah. / 我猜……如果我有几条干裤子的话我今天可能会出去……但还是算了吧。",
        "Rainy_Night_0": "Hmm... seems like a good night to microwave a few pizza rolls. / 嗯……今晚似乎很适合用微波炉做几个披萨卷。#$e#Some people like to cook them in the oven, but it just takes too long for me. Plus I like that squishy texture.$h / 有些人喜欢用烤炉做，但是对我来说那太慢了。另外我喜欢那种黏糊糊的口感。$h",
        "Good_8": "I don't really feel like doing work today. Maybe I'll see what's on TV. / 我今天没什么工作的心情。也许我应该看电视。",
        "Good_3": "I'm in a great mood today... The Tunnelers won big last night.$h / 我今天心情很好……隧道掘进队昨晚赢大了。$h",
        "Bad_7": "Farm-life is actually really boring. What am I doing here?$s / 农场生活其实真的挺无聊的。我到底在这干嘛？$s",
        "Rainy_Night_4": "Tip-tappa-tip-tappa-tip... I'm starting to feel thirsty.$6 / 滴答滴答滴……我开始觉得渴了。$6",
        "Neutral_2": "Why don't you tell me about your day when we're in bed tonight? I'm kind of busy right now... / 等我们今晚躺在床上的时候再给我讲讲你的一天吧？我现在有点忙……",
        "Rainy_Day_2": "Here... take this.[346 174 303 305 215] / 来……这个拿去吧。[346 174 303 305 215]#$e#I bought some of those a while ago and they're almost expired... / 我前一段时间买了一些，现在都快要过期了……",
        "Outdoor_4": "Hey, @. You were sleeping like a baby so I slipped out of bed and went for a morning walk around the farm. Everything looks fine. / 嘿，@。你熟睡得像个小孩一样，于是我从床上溜了出去，在农场里散了一会步。一切看起来都很好。",
        "OneKid_0": "It's weird, when I was younger I swore I'd never have a kid. I wonder what happened to me?$6 / 很奇怪，当我年轻的时候，我发誓我不要孩子。我不知道自己到底怎么了？$6",
        "Neutral_8": "Ugh... clean, clean, clean. Sweep, sweep, sweep. Bathe. Cook. Make the bed... Oh, well. Life's alright. / 呃……清扫、清扫、清扫。打扫，打扫，打扫。洗澡。做饭。整理床铺……哎，好吧。生活就是这样。",
        "summer_27": "What are your plans for the fall? I'm going to try and incorporate more wine into my diet. / 你秋天的计划是什么？我要试着把葡萄酒融入我的饮食。",
        "Rainy_Day_3": "Buhh... I don't feel like being productive today. / 哎……我今天感觉没什么动力。",
        "Rainy_Night_1": "The tip-tappa-tip of the rain takes me to a different time... a different place. / 雨水的滴答声仿佛把我带到了一个不同的时间……不同的地点。",
        "TwoKids_3": "*Sigh*... If only we could send the kids off to Joja work-camp for a season... / *唉*……如果我们能送孩子去Joja工作营干一段时间就好了……#$e#I'm just kidding.$h / 我只是在开玩笑。$h",
        "Outdoor_0": "I didn't sleep well last night so I'm hoping this fresh air will get the juices flowing. / 我昨晚睡得不好所以我希望这新鲜空气能促进果汁流动。#$e#What juices, you ask? Heh... you're weird.$h / 你问什么果汁？呵……你真奇怪。$h",
        "Rainy_Night_3": "I like gloomy weather, but I feel kinda bad for the hens. / 我喜欢阴天，但我感觉母鸡们有点可怜。",
        "winter_28": "Well, another year gone by... I look a little older, but that's about all.$6 / 好吧，又一年过去了……我看起来又老了一点，但仅此而已。$6",
        "winter_1": "Any big plans this winter? I'll probably end up watching a lot of TV and just hanging out around the house. / 今年冬天有什么大计划？我可能会整天看电视，在家里悠闲地度过。",
        "Rainy_Day_4": "@, should I do something useful today?... or just nap forever? / @，我今天该干点什么实事吗？……还是永远睡下去？",
        "fall_17": "I'm starting to really feel my age... and I'm not comfortable with that at all. / 我真的开始感觉到自己变老了……我对此一点都不开心。",
        "Bad_5": "Look, I just want to be alone. Why don't you go outside and do your own thing for a while? / 拜托，我只想自己一个人呆着。你为什么不去外面做你自己的事情？",
        "Indoor_Night_3": "Buh... I wish I was six inches taller and a whole lot smarter... / 哎……我希望自己能再长高 6 英寸并且再聪明一点……#$e#You like me for who I am? I still have a hard time understanding that... / 你就喜欢我这样的么？我还是很难理解……",
        "Good_0": "*Sniff*... *sniff*... mmm... what's that wonderful fragrance you're wearing? Eau de pepperoni?$6 / *闻*……*闻*……嗯……你身上那美妙的香味是什么？意大利辣肉肠香水？$6",
        "Outdoor_3": "Ooohh... my tongue is swollen from eating too many pepper poppers.$s / 噢……吃了太多辣椒波普尔奶酪面包，我的舌头都肿了。$s",
        "Good_6": "Ah... this is the life. No responsibilities, Tunnelers game tonight, fridge stocked with all the goodies a guy could need.$h / 啊……这简直就是完美的生活。不需要负责任，晚上有隧道掘进队的比赛，冰箱里塞满了我想要的一切。$h",
        "Indoor_Day_4": "I may keep to myself a lot, and I may seem unhappy sometimes... but I do appreciate all the work you do. I'm a lucky guy.$6 / 我可能会经常闷不作声，有时我可能看起来不太开心……但我很感激你付出的所有努力。我真是个幸运的家伙。$6",
        "Indoor_Night_2": "Ughh... *gurgle*... I feel a little bloated... oof... too much Joja all-purpose dipping sauce. / 呃……*嗝*……我觉得Joja万能蘸酱有点……太多了……",
        "Good_1": "You're a lot better-looking than me, you know that?$h / 你知道自己比我漂亮得多了吗？$h",
        "Neutral_3": "Working at Joja was a drag, but at least I got to interact with people occasionally. / 在 Joja 商场工作是很累，但至少我还偶尔与人互动。",
        "fall_15": "I'll be helping Marnie with the animals at tomorrow's fair, like usual. You should just kick back and have some fun.$6 / 我会像往常一样在明天的市集上帮助玛妮照顾动物。你应该休息休息，好好玩一下。$6",
        "Neutral_6": "If you need to go see your friends in town, go ahead. I'm happy in the company of the TV and a couple of tall boys. / 如果你要去镇里看你的朋友就去吧。有电视和几个高个子男孩陪我就很高兴了。",
        "Good_2": "The name 'Shane' means 'Gift from Yoba'... What a joke. / “谢恩”这个名字的意思是“来自由巴的礼物”……真是个笑话。",
        "Rainy_Day_0": "I hope Jas and Marnie are doing alright without me. / 但愿我不在的时候贾斯和玛妮也过得很好。#$e#I'm not too worried... Jas is old enough now to take care of the animals on her own. / 我不是太担心的………贾斯现在长大了，可以自己照顾这些动物了。",
        "funLeave_Shane": "I'm going to go out today, alright? / 我今天要出门，好吧？",
        "spring_1": "Ooo... my throbbing head. How many did I have last night? / 噢……我的头好痛。昨晚我到底喝了多少？",
        "spring_23": "Oh, right. It's the flower dance tomorrow. Hey, if it makes you happy, I'm happy. / 噢，对了。明天是花舞节。嘿，如果你觉得开心，那我也开心。",
        "Outdoor_1": "Sometimes I stop and realize that I'm nothing more than a bag of juicy, squishy flesh. / 有时我会突然意识到自己只不过是一副柔弱的血肉之躯。#$e#But hey... that's just fine... what's life, anyway?$h / 但是呢……那也很好……反正生活就是如此呀？$h",
        "Indoor_Day_3": "*smooch*... Mmm, it tastes like someone's been nibbling on pizza rolls.$6 / *亲吻*……嗯，味道像是有人刚吃过披萨卷。$6",
        "Indoor_Day_1": "Hey. Take this... I put a bit too much in the microwave. [195 215 206] / 嘿。拿着……我往微波炉里放太多了。[195 215 206]#$e#Sorry if it's squishy. / 如果黏糊糊的，可别介意啊。",
        "Indoor_Day_0": "Buh... sometimes life feels like a slow, gray blur... know what I mean? / 哎……生活有时候就像是一团缓慢而模糊的景象……懂我的意思吗？",
        "TwoKids_2": "Ugh... %kid2 is being a little brat today. Must've gotten that from me... / 呃……%kid2今天有点调皮。一定是传我的代……",
        "Rainy_Day_1": "You know what? I think I've lost some weight since moving in with you.$6 / 你知道吗？自从与你在一起后，我的体重已经减轻了一些。$6",
        "Outdoor_2": "When I stop and think about it... I'm in a good place. My life is pretty nice.$6 / 如果我仔细想想的话……我现在处境挺不错的。我过得很好。$6",
        "OneKid_3": "Papa Shane reporting for duty...$6 / 谢恩爸爸报到……$6#$e#Buh... I've become corny in my old age. / 哎……我已经变得又老又土了。",
        "Neutral_4": "What, you want me to clean the dishes? I'll do it... eventually... / 什么，你想让我洗盘子？我会洗的……迟早吧……",
        "OneKid_1": "Let's make sure to give %kid1 lots of eggs... Baby's gotta grow those legs! / 我们一定要给%kid1吃很多鸡蛋……这样宝宝才会长得很高！",
        "spring_12": "The egg festival is probably my favorite... you know how I am, I go crazy for anything to do with chickens.$h / 蛋蛋节日大概是我最喜欢的节日……你了解我的，与鸡有关的任何事情都能让我为之疯狂。$h",
        "Indoor_Night_0": "I'm just gonna have a couple more beers before closing my eyes for the night. / 我只想在上床睡觉之前再多喝一些啤酒。",
        "patio_Shane": "Charlie's doing well.$8 / 查理过得很好。$8",
        "TwoKids_0": "I already fed the kids two bowls of pizza puffs cereal. They'll be full for a while. / 我已经喂了孩子们两碗比萨泡芙麦片。他们这会儿不会饿了。",
        "TwoKids_1": "I'll be honest... two kids is enough for me. / 老实说……两个孩子对我来说足够了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Strings/schedules/Abigail",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "Sun.000": "We're hiding in here so we don't have to talk to anyone. / 我们藏在这里，这样就不用和任何人说话。",
        "spring_4.000": "Ugh... I have a doctor's appointment later.$s / 啊……我一会儿约了医生。$s",
        "marriage_Mon.000": "Dad seems to be doing okay without me around. / 没有我在身边，爸爸似乎还好。",
        "marriage_Mon.002": "Urgh... I still can't beat it by myself.$s / 呃……我还是不能独自打通它。$s",
        "marriage_Fri.000": "What's up, @? I'm just saying hi to the mom. / 怎么了，@？我只是在跟妈妈打招呼。",
        "spring_4.002": "How much longer do you need, doc? I'm hungry.$s / 还需要多久啊，医生？我饿了。$s",
        "marriage_Fri.001": "It's nice to see the ol' gang again. Nothing's changed.$h / 再次看到老朋友们很高兴。什么都没变。$h",
        "spring_4.001": "I'm just here for my annual check-up! Don't worry, I'm not preg... I mean, I'm not sick! Heh.$9 / 我只是来做年度体检的！别担心，我没有怀……我是说，我没生病！呵呵。$9",
        "marriage_Mon.001": "Hey, @. I like to relax here... it's so peaceful. / 嘿，@。我喜欢在这里放松……如此宁静。",
        "winter_15.000": "This is so mysterious... I love it! / 太神秘了……我喜欢！"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Strings/schedules/Alex",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "Sun.000": "%Alex is completely engrossed in the game. He doesn't notice your presence. / %亚历克斯完全沉浸在游戏里，他没有注意到你的到来。",
        "marriage_Mon.000": "I'm going to hang out here all day. My grandparents aren't getting any younger... / 我一整天都将在这里待着。我的祖父母都不再年轻了……",
        "summer_16.001": "Yeah, yeah... I'm good, doc. Just tape it up, okay? / 嗯，嗯……我很好，医生。就帮我上一下绷带，行吗？",
        "Sun.000_married": "Hey, @! You can watch the game with us if you want, but no pressure if you're busy. / 嘿，@！如果你愿意的话，可以和我们一起观看比赛，你忙的话就拒绝吧，没啥大不了的。",
        "summer_16.000": "Hi. Eh, I just twisted my ankle. Seeing if I can get it taped. / 你好。呃，我刚刚把脚扭了。能不能帮我上一下绷带。",
        "winter_17.000": "Have you seen the mermaid show? It's my favorite... / 你见过美人鱼秀吗？那是我的最爱……"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Strings/schedules/Caroline",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "fall_25.002": "Excuse me, I have to say some things to Doctor Harvey in private...$u / 抱歉，我需要和哈维医生私下谈谈……$u",
        "Sun.000": "It was the previous owners who built the altar room. We aren't religious, but we let the other townsfolk use it if they want. / 前任房主建造了祭坛室。我们不信宗教，但我们会让其他镇民随意使用。",
        "Fri.000": "Finally... A little time to myself. / 终于……有了一点儿自己的时间。",
        "Tue.002": "Mmff... I think I've earned some cookies today. *crunch*. / 唔……我想我今天能吃点儿饼干了。*咂巴*。",
        "winter_16.000": "I'm getting all my holiday shopping done tonight! Let me know if you see Pierre coming... / 今晚，我要完成全部假日购物！如果你看到皮埃尔来了，告诉我……",
        "Tue.000": "Hmm... Should I wear something special to the aerobics meet-up today? / 唔……嗯……我是不是应该为今天的有氧运动聚会特意打扮下？",
        "fall_25.001": "You're here to see the doctor too? What happened? / 你也是来看医生的？发生了什么？",
        "fall_25.000": "It's my annual check-up today. At least I don't have to walk very far. / 今天是我年度体检的日子。至少我不用走很远。",
        "Tue.001": "You're looking really fit, Jodi! Those dumbbells do wonders, don't they? / 你看起来好健康啊，乔迪！练哑铃真的很管用吧？"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Strings/schedules/Clint",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "winter_16.001": "I'm seeing the doctor about my lungs... breathing in all that coal dust can't be good. / 我要去找医生检查我的肺……在总是吸入煤灰的环境里肯定好不了。",
        "winter_16.000": "I have a doctor's appointment today, so if you need to buy anything you'd better hurry. / 我今天约了医生，你想买东西就要赶紧了。",
        "winter_16.002": "How do my lungs sound, doc? Sometimes they make a rattling sound when I exhale. / 我的肺怎么样了，医生？有时候我呼吸都会像破风箱一样。",
        "winter_15.000": "I have a doctor's appointment tomorrow... Maybe the mermaid show will calm my nerves? But what if they think I'm ogling... *gulp* / 我明天约了看医生……或许美人鱼秀能让我平静下来？但是，如果他们认为我在嘀咕……*咽口水*……会怎么样？"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Strings/schedules/Demetrius",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "winter_16.000": "I highly recommend the submarine tour. There are some very fascinating creatures living in the deep ocean. / 我强烈推荐潜艇之旅。在深海中生活一些非常迷人的生物。",
        "summer_25.000": "The colder season is coming up so I'm here to get my flu vaccine. / 寒冷的季节就要来了，我是来打流感疫苗的。",
        "summer_25.001": "Doctor Harvey, have you read the latest 'Biology and Medicine'? There's an article I think you'd be interested in. / 哈维医生，你读了最新一期的《生物医学》吗？里面有篇文章你可能会感兴趣。"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Strings/schedules/Elliott",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "summer_9.000": "Hello there. What brings you to this terrible place? / 你好啊。什么风把你吹到这鬼地方来的？",
        "marriage_Mon.000": "Hello, @. I'm just watching the waves from here. / 您好，@。我只是在这里观看浪涛。",
        "summer_9.001": "My back has been hurting, doctor... you know, with all the hunching over to write my novel. / 医生，我的背好疼啊……因为我老是弓着背写小说。",
        "winter_17.000": "A fleet of exotic merchants, traveling the world in search of riches beyond imagination... what an adventure! / 一队异国商人在世界各地搜寻超乎想象的财富……多么辉煌的冒险！"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Strings/schedules/Emily",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "marriage_Mon.002": "Gus seems to have problems organizing everything without me around. / 没有我在身边，格斯好像组织任何事情都会出问题。",
        "Sandy_Birthday_Lake": "Phew... It's hot!#$e#It seems like a good day to go swimming.#$e#It's probably nice and cool in there.$h / 呼……真热！#$e#今天挺适合去游泳的。#$e#肯定会很凉爽！$h",
        "Sandy_Birthday_Bones": "Can you believe this place?#$e#This is so mysterious... / 这是什么奇妙的地方？#$e#太神秘了……",
        "marriage_Fri.002": "Friday nights are busy, so I'm just helping out for old time's sake. It's fun!$h / 星期五晚上是高峰期，所以我顾及旧情也来帮帮忙。真有意思！$h",
        "marriage_Mon.000": "It's good to visit the old house. It's full of memories. / 拜访老房子是很棒的事情。它充满了回忆。",
        "Sandy_Birthday_Greeting": "Hi Sandy! I got this gift for you. I hope you like it!$h / 你好呀，桑迪！这是我给你准备的礼物。希望你喜欢！$h",
        "winter_11.001": "Doctor, I'd like to go with the 'natural remedy' if possible. / 医生，如果可能的话，我想用“自然疗法”。",
        "Sandy_Birthday_Bye": "That was fun!#$b#I wanna come back soon!$h / 太开心了！#$b#真想快点再来玩！$h",
        "marriage_Fri.000": "I'm just looking for mermaids. / 我正寻找美人鱼。",
        "Sandy_Birthday_Hangout": "I'm so glad to have a day off from work!$h#$e#I feel content. / 今天终于可以不用干活了！$h#$e#我满足了。",
        "marriage_Fri.001": "I come here to smell the fruit. / 我来这儿闻水果的味道。",
        "Fri.000": "What a lovely loom. I'm in heaven right now. / 好可爱的织布机啊。我肯定是在天堂里。",
        "Sandy_Birthday_Camel": "I love being around animals.#$e#This world is full of spirits and magic. / 我喜欢和动物待在一起。#$e#这个世界充斥着幽灵与魔法。",
        "winter_11.000": "Most of us visit the doctor for a yearly check-up. / 大多数人都会找医生做年检。",
        "marriage_Mon.001": "I'm trying to get a good walk in today. My legs feel like cannelloni. / 今天我打算多走走。感觉腿都要软了。",
        "winter_15.000": "I think this boat's my favorite. It's so unique! / 我认为这条船是我的最爱。它如此独特！"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Strings/schedules/Evelyn",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "2.001": "Oh dear, is it an emergency? Why are you here?$s / 哦，亲爱的，你怎么来了？难道要看急诊？$s",
        "23.001": "Could you check his lungs? He's been wheezing lately. / 能检查一下他的肺部吗？他最近总喘不过气。",
        "23.000": "Now now, dear... It's important that Doctor Harvey takes a good look at you. He's a nice young man! Behave yourself, for your dear old wife's sake. / 哦，亲爱的……最好让哈维医生给你检查一下。他可是个不错的小伙子！行为端重点，就算是看在你老妻的份上。",
        "Thu.000": "This place is full of memories for me. Thank you so much for restoring it.$h / 我在这里留下了好多回忆。谢谢你把这里恢复原状。$h",
        "2.000": "When you get to be my age you have to see the doctor more often. / 等你到我这个年纪，就要经常看医生了。",
        "winter_17.000": "This is one of the newer traditions in Pelican Town... but we've taken to it rather quickly. Haven't we, George? / 虽然这是鹈鹕镇的新传统之一……但我们已相当迅速地接受了这一传统。乔治，是吧？"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Strings/schedules/George",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "Sun.001": "Hehehe... I skipped church to come here! I hope Yoba isn't too angry with me.$h / 嘻嘻嘻……我没做礼拜就来这里了！希望由巴不要太生气。$h",
        "Sun.000": "I've never been religious but hey... I'm old. / 我从没信过教，不过……我老了。",
        "23.000": "Hmmpph... The wife's making me go to the clinic today. / 哼哼……老婆叫我今天去诊所看看。",
        "23.001": "*grumble*... Good for nothing doctors... *grumble* / *嘟囔*……没用的医生……*嘟囔*",
        "23.002": "Well how much longer do I have, Doc? / 那你说我还剩下多长时间，医生？",
        "winter_17.000": "I'm just here for the free coffee. / 我只是为喝免费咖啡才来这里的。"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Strings/schedules/Gus",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "Sun.000": "Hey @. Sorry... the bar's closed until the game's over. / 嘿，@。不好意思……游戏结束前酒吧不会开放。",
        "fall_4.001": "It's my liver, isn't it Doctor? I can see it on your face. *Sigh*... I really need to cut back on that sweet, delicious Stardew Valley wine.$s / 是肝出问题了吧，医生？我从你脸上瞧出来的。*唉*……我真该少喝点香甜可口的星露谷红酒了。$s",
        "fall_4.000": "Seeing the doctor makes me nervous... What if I only have a few years left? I'm not at peace with the world yet! / 看医生总是让我紧张得要死……要是我活不久了怎么办？这个世界我还没待够呢！",
        "Mon.000": "I'm getting some supplies for the saloon. Pierre's got the good stuff.$h / 我要给酒馆进点货。皮埃尔店里的商品就很不错。$h"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Strings/schedules/Haley",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "winter_16.001": "The cold air isn't so bad if you bundle up!$h / 天气冷只要多穿一点就没事了！$h",
        "rain.000": "The weather's too horrible to get out of bed. / 这天气太糟了，不宜起床。",
        "marriage_Mon.000": "Hi, honey! I'm mostly just here to visit Emily. / 嗨，甜心！我来这里是为了探望艾米丽。",
        "winter_9.000": "It's nothing serious... I'm just here for my annual check-up. / 没什么……我只是来做年度体检的！",
        "winter_16.000": "It's too cold to get out of bed. / 太冷了，不想起床。",
        "winter.000": "It's too cold to get out of bed. / 天气冷得我不想起床。",
        "winter_9.001": "Well... my nose has been a little runny, Doctor. But otherwise I'm doing fine! / 嗯……医生，只是有点流鼻涕。除此以外都很好！"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Strings/schedules/Harvey",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "Fri.000": "This stuff can definitely be incorporated into a healthy diet. / 这东西肯定能纳入健康饮食。",
        "marriage_Mon.000": "Hi! I'm just shopping for some essentials, so I can continue to cook healthy meals for us. / 嗨！我只是在购买一些必需品，这样我就可以继续为我们烹调健康美食。",
        "Sat.000": "I'm just putting away these groceries. / 我正准备把这些食品储存起来。",
        "marriage_Mon.001": "The sound of running water is relaxing for me. / 流水的声音让我感到心旷神怡。",
        "Fri.001": "I'm just putting away these groceries. / 我正准备把这些食品储存起来。",
        "marriageJob.000": "Hi Honey. What are you doing at the clinic?#$e#Ah, you just came to see me. That's nice.$h / 嗨，甜心！你来诊所干嘛？#$e#啊，你是来看我的吧。真贴心。$h",
        "winter_15.000": "Winter can be a dreary season, but events like this make it a little brighter! / 冬季可能个沉闷的季节，但是像这样的活动能让它变得明亮！"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Strings/schedules/Jas",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "winter_18.001": "Can you show me how this tool works, Doctor Harvey? / 哈维医生，能告诉我这东西怎么用吗？",
        "winter_15.001": "I wish I was old enough to see the mermaid show...$s / 我希望我已到了可以看到美人鱼秀的年龄……$s",
        "winter_18.000": "I have to visit the doctor today, but I'm not afraid! / 我今天要去看医生，不过我不怕！",
        "spring.000": "1... 2... 3... 4... Oh no! I messed up again. / 1……2……3……4……哎呀！我又搞砸了。",
        "summer.000": "1... 2... 3... 4... Here comes a wave! *giggle*$h / 1……2……3……4……又来了一个巨浪！*咯咯*$h",
        "winter_15.000": "1... 2... 3... 4... Oh no! I messed up again. / 1……2……3……4……哦，不！我又搞砸了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Strings/schedules/Jodi",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "spring_11.000": "Vincent hates going to the doctor more than anything, but he'll just have to deal with it. / 文森特最讨厌去看医生了，但不管如何他还是得去检查。",
        "spring_11.003": "Vincent was very brave at the doctor's today. I'm proud of him. / 文森特今天在医生那里表现得非常勇敢。我为他感到骄傲。",
        "spring.000": "Shhh... he's asleep. / 嘘……他睡着了。",
        "spring_11.001": "Be brave, Vincent. Think of your father. / 勇敢一点，文森特。想想你的父亲。",
        "spring_11.002": "Doctor Harvey? I'm worried about Vincent's height. Isn't he a little short for his age? / 哈维医生？我有点担心文森特的个头。在这个年纪的小孩中，他会不会矮了点？",
        "spring_18.000": "Hey! You can't just barge into a private appointment!$u / 嘿！你怎么能打断别人的私人预约！$u",
        "Tue.000": "Ohhh... My arms feel like gelatin... $s / 噢……我的手臂像凝胶一样软……$s",
        "winter_17.000": "It must be so thrilling to travel the world like they do... *sigh*... / 像他们一样周游世界一定很刺激……*叹息*……"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Strings/schedules/Leah",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "spring_16.001": "Do I look healthy, Doctor Harvey? / 我看起来健康吗，哈维医生？",
        "spring_16.000": "Hi. Here to see the doctor? / 你好。来看医生的吗？",
        "marriage_Mon.000": "Hello, @. I'm just enjoying the fresh air for a while. I was starting to get cabin fever at home. / 您好，@。我只是在享受一会儿新鲜空气。我在家里待得都要患幽闭症了。",
        "winter_15.000": "Hmmm... a Lupini original? Not bad... / 嗯……卢皮尼的原作？不错……"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Strings/schedules/Leo",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "tent": "We don't mind the rain too much, but it's nice to dry off in here sometimes. / 我们不是很在意下雨，不过有时候在这里晒晒干也挺不错。",
        "school": "Can't talk right now, @. I have to really focus... / @，我现在没空聊天。我得集中注意力……",
        "winter.000": "It's going to take a while, but I'm trying to get through all the books in the library.#$b#I have a lot of catching up to do...$s / 我要翻遍图书馆里的每一本书，应该会花上很长时间。#$b#我还要做很多事情才能赶上……$s",
        "dinner": "Oh, are you hungry? I already finished all the food...$u / 啊，你觉得饿吗？我已经把饭菜都吃掉了……$u",
        "winter_15.000": "I just like looking at the lights.#$b#It reminds me of something, long, long ago...$s / 我喜欢盯着灯看。#$b#会让我会回想起很久以前的事情……$s"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Strings/schedules/Lewis",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "3.000": "I'm just here to make sure all of Marnie's business needs are met. / 我来只是为了确保玛妮的经营需求得到满足。",
        "6.000": "I'm here to collect Clint's business tax. / 我是来向克林特收税的。",
        "fall_9.000": "Erm... Doctor Harvey? This is completely confidential, right? / 呃……哈维医生？你一定会保密的吧？",
        "6.001": "The library is one of Pelican Town's greatest features. It's funded with the taxes we collect from local business. / 图书馆是鹈鹕镇的最大特色之一。是用本地的商务税收投资建的。",
        "1.000": "Well, the fish certainly smells fresh this season. / 嗯，这季节的鱼闻起来很新鲜啊。",
        "winter_16.000": "You know, I've purchased some of my favorite items from this market... / 如你知道，我从这个市场上买了些我最喜欢的东西……",
        "Tue.000": "I do all my grocery shopping here.$h / 食品杂货什么的我都来这买。$h",
        "15.000": "I like to check in with the local businesses and see how they're doing. / 我喜欢检查当地的生意，看看他们做的怎么样。"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Strings/schedules/Linus",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "winter_15.000": "These people are travelers, like me... I feel a connection. But I'm okay just staying here to listen and watch. / 这些人都是旅客，像我一样……我感到有某种缘份。但只是呆在这里倾听和观察，我也能接受。",
        "winter.000": "Even someone like me needs to warm up indoors now and then. / 即使是我也要时不时到室内暖一暖。"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Strings/schedules/Marnie",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "winter_18.001": "We're here for a 1:30pm appointment. / 我们约在了下午一点半。",
        "fall_18.000": "Erm... Doctor Harvey? This is completely confidential, right? / 呃……哈维医生？你一定会保密的吧？",
        "winter_18.000": "I think Jas actually likes going to the doctor. What an unusual little girl. / 我觉得贾斯挺喜欢看医生的。真是不寻常的女孩。",
        "winter_16.000": "Oohh... Fine purple silk. You can't find that at JojaMart! / 哦哦……精美的紫绸。你在 Joja 超市可没法买到！",
        "Tue.000": "I'm going to sleep well tonight.$h / 今晚可以睡个好觉了。$h",
        "winter_18.002": "Erm... Doctor Harvey? When you give her the shots, can we have two lollipops? / 呃……哈维医生？你什么时候给她打针呢？我们能要两根棒棒糖吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Strings/schedules/Maru",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "marriageJob.001": "It's nice for you to visit me.$h / 很高兴你来看我。$h",
        "marriage_Mon.000": "Hey! Mom seems to be doing okay without my help. She's a tough lady. / 嘿！没有我的帮助，妈妈似乎也能做得很好。她是一名坚强的女性。",
        "marriage_Mon.001": "Dad's making good progress on his experiment. / 爸爸的实验取得了长足进展。",
        "marriageJob.002": "I'm almost off work... / 我快下班了……",
        "marriage_Mon.002": "I hope Penny decides to get married some day. / 我希望潘妮能早日结婚。",
        "winter_16.000": "Wow, the tech on this thing is amazing! / 哇，这件事上，科技真神奇！",
        "marriageJob.000": "I'm at work, honey! Don't let the doctor see. / 我在工作，甜心！不要让医生看见。",
        "summer.000": "It's hard to really grasp the scale of the universe.$8 / 想理解宇宙的规模真的很难。$8"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Strings/schedules/Pam",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "spring_25.000": "*grumble*... Doctor know-it-all... *grumble*$4 / *嘟囔*……自以为无所不知的医生……*嘟囔*$4",
        "spring_25.001": "How much do I drink every day? What kind of a question is that?$u / 我每天喝了多少酒？这算哪门子问题？$u"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Strings/schedules/Penny",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "winter_4.000": "I have an appointment at the clinic this afternoon. / 我约好今天下午去诊所。",
        "rain2.000": "I'm going to go inside, I just wanted a quiet moment. / 我要进去了，只想享受片刻安宁。",
        "marriage_Mon.000": "Hi, honey! I'm just doing some shopping. / 嗨，甜心！我只是在购物。",
        "marriage_Mon.001": "Don't worry, I'm using my own money to buy this. / 别担心，我用我自己的钱买的。",
        "marriage_Mon.002": "I wonder if Maru will get married some day? / 不知道玛鲁是否会结婚？",
        "winter_4.001": "Hey! A little privacy, please?$a / 嘿！能给一点隐私吗？$a",
        "marriageJob.000": "Hi, honey. It's nice of you to visit me at work.$h / 嗨，甜心！你来探望我工作真是太好了。$h",
        "winter_15.000": "Can you smell that? The air is so spicy here... / 你能闻到吗？这里的空气真辛辣……"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Strings/schedules/Pierre",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "Fri.000": "I've been working hard all week. I deserve a little relaxation on a Friday night. / 我整周都很卖力。周五晚上放松一下有何不可。"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Strings/schedules/Robin",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "summer_18.001": "Nothing bad to report, Doc. I feel as healthy as ever. / 没什么大碍，医生。我感觉跟以前一样好。",
        "winter_16.000": "My favorite thing is seeing the boats. The creaking sound of the wood is strangely comforting. / 我爱做的事，就是看到这些船。木头吱吱作响，会奇怪地令人感到舒心。",
        "Tue.000": "We meet every week to encourage each other to stay healthy. / 我们每周都会见面，鼓励对方保持健康。",
        "summer_18.000": "What's a healthy young person like you doing here? / 你这么健康的年轻人来这干嘛？"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Strings/schedules/Sam",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "marriage_Fri.001": "Sorry, honey. I'm trying to concentrate here... $7 / 甜心，对不起。我在尝试集中精神……$7",
        "fall_11.001": "I'm a healthy boy, doc. Can I go now? This is boring. / 我是个健康的小孩，医生。我现在可以走了吗？好无聊啊。",
        "rain2.000": "Nothing like an ice cold Joja Cola on a sopping wet day, huh?#$e#Just kidding. Hehehe.$h / 在这湿淋淋的日子里，来一瓶透心凉的 Joja 可乐再好不过了吧？#$e#说笑呢，哈哈哈。$h",
        "marriage_Mon.000": "Mom seems okay. A little overworked, maybe. / 妈妈似乎还好。也许有点过度劳累。",
        "marriage_Mon.001": "Vincent seems a little lonely without me around. I used to play with him a lot. / 没有我在身边，文森特似乎有点落寞。我曾经经常和他一起玩。",
        "fall_11.002": "I just got out of the doctor's office. Completely healthy and vigorous, just as I expected.$h / 我刚从医生办公室出来。完全健康且精力充沛，跟我预计的一样。$h",
        "marriage_Fri.000": "Don't tell my mom... but I really just came over for a free lunch.$h / 不要告诉我妈妈……但我真的只是过来吃免费午餐的。$h",
        "winter_17.000": "Maybe if all else fails, I'll become a submarine captain. That might be cool. / 或许如果其它路都走不通，我会成为一名潜艇艇长。这可能很酷。",
        "fall_11.000": "I gotta go visit Uncle Doctor today... Great.$7 / 今天我得去看医生大叔了……非常好。$7"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Strings/schedules/Sandy",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "Sandy_Birthday_Hangout": "How's that Stardew Valley weather right now?#$e#The flowers there smell lovely.$h / 星露谷的天气怎么样了？#$e#那里的花闻起来很香。$h",
        "Sandy_Birthday_Camel": "I think she sells some rare products. / 她好像是在卖一些稀有的商品。",
        "Sandy_Birthday_Bones": "Strange, isn't it? / 是不是很奇怪？",
        "Sandy_Birthday_Greeting": "Oh, Emily! I was hoping you'd show up!$h#$b#I was actually feeling a little lonely this morning.#$e#But I'm glad you're here!$h / 啊，艾米丽！我正想着你什么时候来呢！$h#$b#我今天早上感觉有点寂寞。#$e#你能来真是太好了！$h",
        "Sandy_Birthday_Bye": "I had a great time.$h#$b#Thanks for being my friend.$h#$e#Come back again any time!$h / 我玩得很开心。$h#$b#谢谢你愿意跟我交朋友。$h#$e#随时再来呀！$h",
        "Sandy_Birthday_Lake": "It always seems to stay a little cooler by the lake.#$e#It's good to get out of the house now and then!$h / 湖边似乎总是凉快一点。#$e#偶尔出去走走也挺好的！$h"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Strings/schedules/Sebastian",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "summer_4.000": "Dammit... I almost forgot. I have to go see Doctor Harvey today. / 该死……我差点忘了。我今天要去看哈维医生。",
        "marriage_Fri.001": "My skills haven't declined... Sam's still just as easy to beat.$h / 我的技术没有下降……山姆还是那么菜。$h",
        "Fri.000": "Should I let Sam win for once? ...nah.$h / 要不要让山姆赢一次呢？……算了吧。$h",
        "rain.000": "The ocean is best enjoyed alone... don't you think? / 观海最好独自一人……你觉得呢？",
        "marriage_Mon.000": "Standing at this spot really makes me want a smoke... but I'm determined to quit now. / 一站在这里我就想抽上一支烟……但我已下决心戒烟了。",
        "summer_4.001": "What are you doing in here? I could've been naked!$a / 你怎么进来了？说不定我没穿衣服呢！$a",
        "marriage_Mon.001": "Mom's face lit up when I walked in. She deserves to be happy.$7 / 我一走进来，妈妈的神色就好了不少。她应该得到幸福。$7",
        "winter_16.000": "I feel more relaxed at night... I might even buy a trinket. / 我在晚上感觉更放松……我甚至可能会购买饰品。",
        "marriage_Fri.000": "I'm going to hang out with my old friends tonight. I'll be home later. / 我今晚要和我的老朋友一起玩。晚点回家。"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Strings/schedules/Shane",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "marriage_Fri.001": "Hmm... I have to say, JojaMart has a much better selection of frozen dinners. / 嗯……我不得不说，Joja 超市有更好的冷冻食品选择。",
        "marriage_Mon.000": "Oh, hey @. Miss me already?$6 / 哦，嘿，@。开始想我了吗？$6",
        "marriage_Fri.003": "I'll just play one more round...$h / 我就再玩一局……$h",
        "marriage_Mon.001": "I'm attached to these woods... lots of memories... / 我在这些树林里留下了……很多的回忆……",
        "marriage_Sun.000": "It smells bad in here. / 这里的味道很难闻。",
        "marriage_Fri.002": "If I don't order a cold one now and then, Gus will go out of business. I'm just doing my civic duty. I'll head home around 10. / 如果我不偶尔买一杯冷啤酒，格斯会歇业的。我只是在履行我的公民义务。我会在 10 点左右回家。",
        "marriage_Sun.001": "I've got cola block... do I pick Joja Classic or Joja Bluu? I might be here a while... / 我手里有可乐块……我应该选经典 Joja 还是蓝色 Joja？我大概要在这里呆一会儿……",
        "marriage_Fri.000": "Don't worry, this is only Joja Cola. / 别担心，这只是 Joja 可乐。",
        "winter_15.000": "I'm taking a night off from the saloon for Jas' sake... / 为了贾斯，我今晚就不去酒吧了……"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Strings/schedules/Vincent",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "spring_11.000": "*sob*... I have to get my shots today.$s / *抽泣*……我今天要打针。$s",
        "spring_11.001": "*gulp*... Mommy, don't make me do it.$s / * 深呼吸 * ……妈咪，别逼我。$s",
        "spring_11.002": "Do I get a lollipop for being so brave? / 我这么勇敢，能不能得到棒棒糖？",
        "winter_16.000": "I wanna ride the boat!! / 我想坐那条船！"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Strings/schedules/Willy",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "spring_9.003": "I need a little warm-me-up to be ready for another cold night on the ocean.$h / 我需要暖暖身，以应对冰冷的海夜。$h",
        "spring_9.002": "Yowch! That hurt, Doc!$s / 嗷！好痛啊，医生！$s",
        "spring_9.000": "I have a doctor's appointment today, so if you need to buy anything you'd better hurry. / 我今天约了医生，你想买东西就要赶紧喽。",
        "winter.000": "I need a little warm-me-up to be ready for another cold night on the ocean.$h / 我需要暖暖身，以应对冰冷的海夜。$h",
        "winter_17.000": "Ah, nothin' like a hot beverage to wind down after a cold, dark day... / 啊，在又冷又暗的一天之后，唯有热饮才能让人放松……",
        "spring_9.001": "Eh, I got a fish hook stuck in my thumb... the Doctor's gonna cut it out. / 呃，有个鱼钩卡在我拇指里面了……医生会把它取出来的。",
        "Fri.000": "Handling salty fish all day makes me real thirsty. / 弄了一整天的咸鱼，我都要渴死了。",
        "Sat.000": "Ah... Nothing's better than kicking back with a cold one after a relaxing day fishing.$h / 啊……大冷天捕鱼之后来一口热酒真是太爽了。$h",
        "winter_16.000": "Have you been on the deep-sea submarine? The captain's an old friend. / 你坐过深海潜艇吗？艇长是老朋友。",
        "winter_15.000": "I can't get me a good night's sleep with that night market going on... eh, but that's okay. I'm flexible. / 由于夜市还没有撤，我无法安然入睡……呃，但没关系。我很灵活。"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Events/AbandonedJojaMart",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "missingBundleComplete": "communityCenter/-2000 -2000/farmer 9 8 3 Junimo 8 8 1/skippable/pause 1000/positionOffset Junimo 0 32/viewport 8 8 true/animate Junimo true true 50 16 17 18 19 20 21 22 23/pause 3000/playSound junimoMeep1/animate Junimo true true 50 0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7/pause 3000/playSound junimoMeep1/animate Junimo true true 50 16 17 18 19 20 21 22 23/pause 3000/fade/viewport -1000 -1000 true/specificTemporarySprite junimoSpotlight/animate Junimo true true 50 0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7/warp Junimo -1000 -1000/pause 3000/playSound junimoMeep1/spriteText 3 \"All the others made it back, except me... \"/playSound junimoMeep1/playMusic none/spriteText 3 \"Now I can go home, too. Thank you! Thank you! \"/pause 1000/animate Junimo true true 100 28 29 30 31/playSound junimoMeep1/pause 5000/screenFlash 1/warp Junimo -9999 -9999/specificTemporarySprite missingJunimoStars/playSound wand/pause 4000/playSound boulderCrack/pause 50/playSound boulderCrack/pause 130/playSound boulderCrack/pause 140/playSound boulderCrack/pause 177/playSound boulderCrack/pause 330/playSound boulderCrack/pause 180/playSound boulderCrack/pause 67/playSound boulderCrack/pause 230/playSound boulderCrack/pause 88/playSound boulderCrack/pause 128/pause 200/playSound boulderCrack/pause 50/playSound boulderCrack/pause 130/playSound boulderCrack/pause 140/playSound boulderCrack/pause 177/playSound boulderCrack/pause 330/playSound boulderCrack/pause 380/playSound boulderCrack/pause 67/playSound boulderCrack/pause 120/playSound boulderCrack/pause 88/playSound boulderCrack/spriteText 4 \"Something good will happen soon... \"/pause 1028/end"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Events/AnimalShop",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "92/e 91/i 78/t 900 1700": "jaunty/13 17/farmer 13 19 0 Marnie 13 14 2/move farmer 0 -1 0/removeQuest 21/removeItem 78/friendship Marnie 100/skippable/emote Marnie 16/speed Marnie 4/move Marnie 0 -1 2/speed Marnie 4/move Marnie 2 0 2/speed Marnie 4/move Marnie 0 3 2/move Marnie -2 0 2/pause 300/speak Marnie \"Oh! You brought the cave carrot! Thank you so much, ${Mr.^Ms.}$ @.$h / 噢！你把山洞胡萝卜拿来了！太感谢你了，@${先生^女士}$。$h\"/pause 500/move farmer 0 -1 1/faceDirection farmer 1/pause 500/playSound woodyStep/addObject 14 17 78/showFrame 35/pause 500/showFrame 6/pause 400/faceDirection farmer 1/move Marnie 1 0 2/emote Marnie 32/speak Marnie \"This looks great... I almost want to eat it myself!$h / 看起来很不错……我都忍不住要自己吃了！$h#$b#...almost. / ……开玩笑呢。\"/faceDirection farmer 1/pause 600/speak Marnie \"I hope it wasn't too much trouble... I really do appreciate it. / 希望没给你添麻烦……十分感激你能帮忙\"/pause 300/removeObject 14 17/pause 400/end dialogue Marnie \"Thanks again for helping me out.$h#$e#...and my goats say 'thanks' too.\"",
        "3900074/f Shane 2000/e 2118991/p Shane": "distantBanjo/27 14/farmer 22 15 1 Jas 30 14 2 Shane -1000 -1000 0/skippable/pause 1000/faceDirection Jas 3/pause 400/jump Jas/pause 1500/move farmer 8 0 0/faceDirection Jas 2/pause 500/speak Jas \"Uncle Shane's in the barn. He said... Uh... He said to tell you he wants to show you something. / 谢恩叔叔在畜棚里。他说…他说要我告诉你他想给你看点东西。\"/pause 500/faceDirection Jas 0/pause 500/playSound doorClose/warp Jas -1000 -1000/pause 800/move farmer 0 -1 0/playSound doorClose/warp farmer -1000 -1000/pause 1600/globalFade/viewport -2000 -2000/changeToTemporaryMap MarnieBarn false/viewport -2000 -2000/addTemporaryActor \"White Chicken\" 16 16 8 5 2 false Animal chicken1/addTemporaryActor \"Blue Chicken\" 16 16 8 9 3 false Animal chicken2/addTemporaryActor \"Blue Chicken\" 16 16 7 7 1 false Animal chicken3/addTemporaryActor \"Blue Chicken\" 16 16 14 11 3 false Animal chicken4/addTemporaryActor \"Blue Chicken\" 16 16 9 11 2 false Animal chicken5/warp Shane 5 3/faceDirection Shane 0/animate Shane false true 500 32 33/viewport 7 3 true/pause 500/move chicken5 -1 0 2 true/pause 1000/move chicken2 3 0 1 true/pause 1500/move chicken4 0 1 2 true/pause 1000/speak Shane \"That should do it...$6 / 应该这样做……$6\"/pause 500/stopAnimation Shane/pause 500/faceDirection Shane 3 true/pause 50/faceDirection Shane 2/pause 1000/move Shane 0 1 2/move Shane 3 0 2/pause 1000/showFrame Shane 30/pause 500/playSound coin/showFrame Shane 29/warp chicken1 -100 -100/pause 500/showFrame Shane 28/move chicken3 0 -1 0 true/pause 1000/move chicken4 0 -1 0/pause 1000/speak Shane \"It's the perfect home for you hens...$8 / 这里很适合你的母鸡居住……$8#$b#We'll have the best eggs in the whole valley!$8 / 我们拥有全镇里最好的鸡蛋！$8#$b#Fresh and healthy, with rich golden yolks. Not like those pale, sickly Joja eggs...$8 / 新鲜而健康，蛋身是营养丰富的金黄色蛋黄。不像 Joja 那些鸡蛋苍白而恶心……$8\"/move chicken2 -1 0 2/pause 1000/move chicken3 0 1 2/emote Shane 28/pause 1500/move chicken4 -1 0 3 true/pause 500/move chicken3 1 0 1 true/move chicken2 1 0 1 true/pause 500/speak Shane \"...*sigh*...$9 / ……*叹息*……$9#$b#...You know, Charlie... I was thinking... $9 / ……你懂的，查理……我曾经想……$9#$b#A guy like me is always teetering on the edge of despair... know what I mean?$9 / 一个像我这样的男孩一直徘徊在绝望的边缘……你懂我说什么吗？$9#$b#...But you and the other hens are going to keep me upright from now on... I know it.$9 / ……但我知道，你和其他母鸡从今往后会帮助我昂首向前……我明白的$9#$b#...$9 / ……$9#$b#What's wrong... too much pressure? *chuckle*$8 / 怎么了……是太多压力了吗？*轻笑*$8\"/pause 500/playSound doorClose/warp Jas 3 8/move Jas 0 -1 0/move Jas 0 -3 1 true/pause 500/warp farmer 3 8/playSound doorClose/move farmer 0 -3 1 false/pause 1000/showFrame Shane 29/pause 500/move chicken2 0 -1 0 true/showFrame Shane 30/warp chicken1 8 5/playSound thudStep/pause 500/move chicken3 -1 0 3/showFrame Shane 0/faceDirection chicken3 2/pause 1000/faceDirection Shane 3/speak Shane \"Hey, @... so, what do you think?$h / 喂，@……那么，你是怎么想的呢？$h\"/animate chicken1 false true 500 16 17/pause 500/animate chicken4 false true 700 16 17/advancedMove chicken2 false 0 -4 -2 0/move farmer 2 0 1/advancedMove chicken3 false -1 0 0 -2/move farmer 0 -1 1/move farmer 2 0 2/faceDirection Shane 2/speak Shane \"My special blue hens... I've been raising them in secret for the last few months.$6 / 我的特别蓝色的母鸡们……最近这几个月我已经开始秘密地饲养它们了。$6\"/faceDirection Shane 3/speak Shane \"I... Well, I won't be living here forever, and I wanted to pass something on to Jas. I've been teaching her how to care for them.$6 / 我……好吧，我不会永远地生活在这里，而且我想要留给贾斯一点东西。我已经在教她怎么照料它们了。$6#$b#...I want to feel like I'm not just a leech on the world. I want to contribute somehow, even in a small way like this. / ……我只想让自己在这世上活得并不仅像是一条水蛭。我想要贡献一些东西，即使是以这样很微不足道的方式。\"/move Jas 3 0 2/faceDirection Shane 2/pause 2000/showFrame Shane 19/pause 500/pause 1000/end",
        "3910974/f Shane 1700/e 3910975/p Shane": "shaneTheme/-2000 -2000/farmer -1000 -1000 1 Marnie 12 14 2 Jas 25 16 3 Shane -1000 -1000 0/skippable/showFrame Jas 22/viewport 13 14 clamp true/pause 2000/playSound doorClose/warp Shane 13 19/move Shane 0 -3 0/pause 500/speak Marnie \"Hi Shane... you look unusually happy today. / 嗨，谢恩…你今天看起来开心地有点不寻常。\"/pause 1000/speak Shane \"You're right... I haven't felt this light since I was a kid.$h / 是的…我从小就没有感受这种心情。$h\"/emote Marnie 8/move Marnie 1 0 2/speak Marnie \"Let me guess... Gus had a clearance sale on canned beer?$u / 让我猜一猜…格斯店里的罐装啤酒做大促销吗？$u\"/pause 500/playSound shwip/faceDirection Shane 1 true/pause 50/faceDirection Shane 2 true/pause 500/textAboveHead Shane \"Good one... / 其中一个…\"/pause 500/showFrame Shane 19/pause 1000/speak Shane \"No, actually. I've been drinking sparkling water instead of beer... and I feel great!$h / 事实上并不是。现在我已经改喝苏打水了…而且我觉得很好喝！$h\"/pause 500/showFrame Shane 0/pause 200/faceDirection Shane 1 true/pause 50/faceDirection Shane 0/speak Shane \"You know, I sometimes forget that I really do have friends, people that care about me. / 你知道的，我有时候会忘记我拥有真心朋友，大家都很关心我。#$b#And it's okay for me to rely on them... it doesn't make me weak. / 让我知道我可以依赖他们…这使我并不那么脆弱。\"/pause 500/emote Marnie 32/viewport move 1 0 6000/move Shane 4 0 2/textAboveHead Marnie \"He looks sharp! / 他看起来很耀眼！\"/move Shane 0 2 1/move Shane 4 0 0/move Shane 0 -2 1/speak Shane \"Hi Jas. I've got something for you.$6 / 嗨，贾斯。我有东西要给你。$6\"/pause 500/showFrame Shane 26/specificTemporarySprite jasGift/playSound coin/pause 500/showFrame Shane 4/emote Jas 8 true/move Jas -2 0 3/pause 800/playSound woodWhack/specificTemporarySprite jasGiftOpen/pause 500/showFrame Jas 24/playSound yoba/pause 2000/speak Jas \"Th... These are real bunny-jewel slippers!!$h / 这…这是真的兔子宝石靴子！！$h\"/pause 200/speed Jas 6/jump Jas/move Jas -1 0 3/showFrame Jas 23/positionOffset Jas -2 1/pause 10/positionOffset Jas -2 0/pause 10/positionOffset Jas -2 0/pause 10/positionOffset Jas -2 0/showFrame Shane 18/pause 10/positionOffset Jas -2 0/pause 10/positionOffset Jas -2 0/pause 10/positionOffset Jas -2 0/pause 10/positionOffset Jas -2 0/pause 10/positionOffset Jas -2 0/pause 10/positionOffset Jas -2 0/pause 10/positionOffset Jas -2 0/pause 10/positionOffset Jas -2 0/pause 10/positionOffset Jas -2 0/pause 10/positionOffset Jas -2 0/pause 10/positionOffset Jas -2 0/pause 10/positionOffset Jas -2 1/pause 2000/viewport -2000 -2000/playMusic none/pause 1000/speak Jas \"B... But these are so expensive!$3 / 但…但这很贵！$3#$b#How did you afford them?$3 / 你是怎么买到的？$3\"/pause 1000/speak Shane \"I've cut back on an expensive habit. I have a lot more spending money now!$h / 我现在已经减少了一些奢侈的习惯。现在我有更多能花的钱了！$h\"/pause 1000/end",
        "3910674/f Shane 1000": "shaneTheme/-2000 -2000/farmer 18 18 1 Marnie 21 14 0 Jas 25 16 2 Shane -1000 -1000 2/skippable/specificTemporarySprite shanePassedOut/viewport 22 8 true/pause 2000/speak Marnie \"Shane? / 谢恩？\"/pause 2000/doAction 21 13/pause 500/move Marnie 0 -7 1/textAboveHead Marnie \"Oh dear... / 噢！亲爱的……\"/doAction 21 13/removeTile 21 13 Buildings/removeTile 21 12 Front/move farmer 3 0 0/faceDirection Jas 3 true/move farmer 0 -10 1/faceDirection Marnie 2/pause 500/speak Marnie \"@... Can you do something? He's out cold.$s / @……你能帮忙吗？ 他在处于人生低潮。$s\"/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 0/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 1/move farmer 3 0 0/faceDirection Marnie 1 true/move farmer 0 -1 1/pause 1000/speak Shane \"buhhh...$7 / 不……$7\"/pause 2000/specificTemporarySprite waterShane/pause 250/playSound wateringCan/pause 1000/specificTemporarySprite waterShaneDone/warp Shane 25 7/textAboveHead Shane \"Whaa..?! / 什……？！\"/jump Shane/shake Shane 2000/showFrame Shane 18/pause 3000/showFrame Shane 0/move farmer -1 0 1/faceDirection Shane 3/speak Marnie \"Shane! What's the matter with you? All you do anymore is mope around your room and drink beer!$s / 谢恩！你怎么了？你所能做的一切就是躲在你的房间忧郁喝啤酒吗！$s\"/move Jas -4 0 0 true/pause 200/faceDirection Shane 2 true/pause 50/faceDirection Shane 1/emote Shane 12/shake Shane 1000/textAboveHead Shane \"... / ……\"/pause 1500/speak Shane \"You wouldn't understand... / 你不懂……\"/pause 1000/textAboveHead Marnie \"I'm worried... / 我担心……\"/move Jas 0 -8 1/speak Marnie \"What's your plan? Don't you ever think about the future? / 你的计划是什么？你想过未来吗？\"/faceDirection Shane 0/textAboveHead Shane \"Plan? / 计划？\"/pause 2000/speak Shane \"Hopefully I won't be around long enough to need a 'plan'... / 希望找到我的人生计划不需要花费很长时间……\"/jump Jas/pause 500/shake Jas 10000/speed Jas 4/textAboveHead Jas \"...*sob*... / ……*呜呜*……\"/move Jas 0 10 2 true/faceDirection Marnie 2/emote Marnie 28 true/faceDirection farmer 3/faceDirection Shane 1 true/pause 50/faceDirection Shane 2/pause 600/move Marnie 0 10 2 true/pause 1000/textAboveHead Shane \"Jas... / 贾斯……\"/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 1/pause 400/showFrame Shane 19/pause 1000/textAboveHead Shane \"I'm sorry... / 对不起……\"/pause 3000/faceDirection Shane 1 true/showFrame Shane 4/pause 500/showFrame Shane 35/playSound thudStep/shake Shane 4000/pause 2000/end"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Events/ArchaeologyHouse",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "1848481/f Elliott 2000/t 1300 1900/n elliottReading": "breezy/14 11/Elliott 14 9 2 Pierre 10 13 1 Caroline 11 13 3 Marnie 11 15 1 Lewis 12 15 3 Sebastian 11 17 2 Abigail 12 18 3 Sam 10 18 1 Leah 15 15 0 Emily 16 16 2 Clint 15 17 1 Jodi 19 13 2 Robin 20 14 3 Demetrius 20 11 3 Maru 10 10 1 Penny 11 9 1 Gus 18 16 0 Shane 19 16 0 Willy 21 11 3 farmer 6 14 1/skippable/move farmer 6 0 0/move farmer 0 -1 0/move Elliott 0 4 3/faceDirection farmer 1/speak Elliott \"@, you made it!$h / @，我成功了！$h#$b#I feel so relieved to be done with my book... it's like an elephant's been lifted off my shoulders. / 写完后我整个人都轻松多了……就像便秘了整个月突然畅通无阻的感觉。\"/pause 800/faceDirection Elliott 2/pause 500/faceDirection Elliott 1/pause 500/faceDirection Elliott 3/pause 500/speak Elliott \"Well, I'd better get started with the reading... Wish me luck.$8 / 我得开始阅读了……祝我好运吧。$8\"/pause 700/move Elliott 0 -4 2/faceDirection farmer 0/pause 500/faceDirection Elliott 1/faceDirection Elliott 2/faceDirection Elliott 3/faceDirection Elliott 2/speak Elliott \"Good afternoon, everyone. / 大家下午好。\"/pause 500/faceDirection Caroline 0 true/faceDirection Emily 0 true/textAboveHead Emily \"Hi! / 嗨！\"/faceDirection Abigail 0/faceDirection Sebastian 0 true/faceDirection Lewis 0/faceDirection Sam 0 true/faceDirection Marnie 0/faceDirection Pierre 0 true/faceDirection Jodi 0/faceDirection Clint 0/speak Elliott \"Ever since I was a young boy, I've dreamt of becoming a writer. / 我从小就想当一位作家。#$b#When the time came for me to leave home and start my own life, I moved here. I was drawn to the peaceful beauty of the valley, and hoped that days of quiet reflection in this idyllic atmosphere would fan the literary flames. / 当我长大出外闯荡时，我就选择了移居到这里来。因为这个山谷的宁静之美深深地吸引住了我。我希望能够在这里获得创作的灵感。\"/showFrame Elliott 32/pause 200/showFrame Elliott 34/fork 958699 mysteryBook/fork 958700 romanceBook/speak Elliott \"After countless hours scribbling at my writing desk, I present to you my first novel: 'The Rise And Fall Of Planet Yazzo'... It's a sci-fi epic spanning thousands of years in an exotic planetary system. / 经过无数个小时在书桌前奋斗后，我给你们带来了我的第一本创作：《亚索行星的兴旺史》……这是一本科幻小说，描述一个遥远的银河系延绵数千年的事迹。\"/animate Elliott false true 1000 33 33 34/pause 500/speak Elliott \"Chapter One. / 第一章。#$b#Commander Yutkin stepped through the golden archway as the airlock snapped shut behind him. Today was his first day on Planet Yazzo, and all 14 of the alliance delegates had been summoned to the Grand Spire... / 于禁指挥官踏上金碧辉煌的走道，身后的气阀门随之关闭。这是他第一次踏上亚索行星，所有 14 位同盟代表都被聚集在宏伟尖塔……\"/playMusic none/globalFade/viewport -100 -100/pause 1000/warp Sebastian -1000 -1000/warp Sam -1000 -1000/warp Abigail -1000 -1000/warp Jodi -1000 -1000/warp Robin -1000 -1000/warp Demetrius -1000 -1000/warp Shane -1000 -1000/warp Maru -1000 -1000/warp Pierre -1000 -1000/warp Caroline -1000 -1000/viewport 14 11 true/pause 1000/speak Elliott \"...And as the 7th moon descended beneath the horizon, the planet of Yazzo would begin its sinister transformation... an event for which Commander Yutkin was completely unprepared. / ……当第七个月地平线沉下时，亚索行星会开始进行邪恶的转变……这是连于禁指挥官都完全没有料到的。\"/stopAnimation Elliott/showFrame Elliott 34/pause 800/speak Elliott \"Well, that concludes my reading. I'll be selling signed copies of the book by the front desk. Thanks for listening!$h / 阅读就到此为止。我会在前台出售亲笔签名版的书本。谢谢收听！$h\"/faceDirection Lewis 3/faceDirection Marnie 1/faceDirection Emily 2 true/faceDirection Clint 1/move Elliott 0 4 3/faceDirection farmer 1/pause 600/speak Elliott \"Well, how was it? / 感觉怎么样？\"/emote farmer 32/speak Elliott \"Thanks. $h / 谢谢。$h#$b#You know, I got the idea for making a sci-fi book from you. Do you remember? / 其实我创造这本小说的灵感是来自于你。你还记得吗？#$b#That's why I've dedicated this book to you...$l / 所以我把这本书献给你……$l\"/move Elliott -1 0 3/emote Elliott 32/pause 1000/end",
        "mysteryBook": "pause 400/speak Elliott \"After countless hours scribbling at my writing desk, I present to you my first book: 'Blue Tower'... It's a mystery novel set in a surreal, dystopian future. / 经过无数个小时在书桌前奋斗后，我给你们带来了我的第一本创作：《蓝塔》……这是一本在未来世界的悬疑小说。\"/animate Elliott false true 1000 33 33 34/pause 500/speak Elliott \"Chapter One. / 第一章。#$b#From the shadows emerged a man, radiating with enigmatic omniscience. 'Good Evening, Mr. Lu,' he said, the corners of his mouth quivering. Lu seemed astonished. 'How did you know my name?' / 阴影中走出一位充满睿智的男子。“下午好，陆先生，”他颤栗着嘴角说道。陆非常惊讶。“你是怎么知道我叫什么名字的？” \"/playMusic none/globalFade/viewport -100 -100/pause 1000/warp Sebastian -1000 -1000/warp Sam -1000 -1000/warp Abigail -1000 -1000/warp Jodi -1000 -1000/warp Robin -1000 -1000/warp Demetrius -1000 -1000/warp Shane -1000 -1000/warp Maru -1000 -1000/warp Pierre -1000 -1000/warp Caroline -1000 -1000/viewport 14 11 true/pause 1000/speak Elliott \"Lu checked Jenu's pockets, then stood up and walked into the bedroom. He quickly found the small golden key that he was looking for and slipped it into his coat pocket. / 陆检查洁努的口袋，然后站起身走进卧室。他很快发现了自己在寻找的黄金小钥匙，然后把它放进自己的外套口袋中。\"/stopAnimation Elliott/showFrame Elliott 34/pause 800/speak Elliott \"Well, that concludes my reading. I'll be selling signed copies of the book by the front desk. Thanks for listening!$h / 阅读就到此为止。我会在前台出售亲笔签名版的书本。谢谢收听$h\"/faceDirection Lewis 3/faceDirection Marnie 1/faceDirection Emily 2 true/faceDirection Clint 1/move Elliott 0 4 3/faceDirection farmer 1/pause 600/speak Elliott \"Well, how was it? / 感觉怎么样？\"/emote farmer 32/speak Elliott \"Thanks. $h / 谢谢。$h#$b#You know, I got the idea for making a mystery from you. Do you remember? / 其实我创造科幻小说的灵感是来自于你？#$b#That's why I've dedicated this book to you...$l / 所以我把这本书献给你……$l\"/move Elliott -1 0 3/emote Elliott 32/pause 1000/end",
        "0/n somethingToDonate/l somethingWasDonated": "libraryTheme/29 12/farmer 22 13 1 Gunther 31 12 2/removeQuest 23/addQuest 24/skippable/pause 1000/showFrame Gunther 4/pause 500/showFrame Gunther 0/pause 500/showFrame Gunther 12/pause 500/showFrame Gunther 0/pause 1000/showFrame Gunther 1/pause 500/speak Gunther \"Abysmal... / 糟透了……#$b#Not a single piece in the entire collection. / 整个收藏里半个都找不到。\"/move farmer 7 0 1/showFrame Gunther 12/pause 800/emote Gunther 16/jump Gunther/pause 800/speak Gunther \"What's this? You found something? Let me see it! / 这是什么？你找到了？让我看看！\"/move farmer 0 -1 1/move farmer 1 0 1/pause 500/playSound coin/animate Gunther false true 500 2 3/pause 3000/speak Gunther \"Remarkable! / 太美妙了！#$b#It's very old. / 这本书很旧了。#$b#I'd love to study this in greater detail... But it is yours. / 我很想深入研究……不过书是你找到的。\"/stopAnimation Gunther/showFrame Gunther 12/pause 1000/speak Gunther \"Hmmm... / 唔……#$b#I've got a favor to ask you. / 我想找你帮个忙。#$b#Would you consider donating any new artifacts or minerals that you find? / 你是否愿意捐献你找到的任何文物或者矿物？#$b#We could make a groundbreaking discovery together! / 我们可以联手制造大新闻！#$b#Oh, and who knows... If you keep donating I might come across some interesting items to send your way. / 而且，如果你一直捐献的话，说不定我会送你一些有趣的物品。\"/pause 1000/showFrame Gunther 0/pause 500/speak Gunther \"Think about it, will you? / 考虑下吧，好吗？#$b#If you decide to donate, just bring the objects to the front desk. / 如果你决定捐献了，就把物品带到前台来。\"/move farmer -3 0 2 true/pause 400/showFrame Gunther 1/proceedPosition farmer/move farmer 0 1 3/move farmer -7 0 3 true/pause 1000/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/end",
        "romanceBook": "pause 400/speak Elliott \"After countless hours scribbling at my writing desk, I present to you my first novel: 'Camellia Station'... It's a romance novel about a train stewardess who falls in love with a traveling architect... / 经过无数个小时在书桌前奋斗后，我带给你我的第一本创作：《茶花车站》……这是一本爱情小说，是关于一位爱上建筑师的火车乘务员……\"/animate Elliott false true 1000 33 33 34/pause 500/speak Elliott \"Chapter One. / 第一章．#$b#'Your ticket, sir?' Ticket collector Gozman extended a gloved hand towards the young commuter. 'Ah, yes. I have it right here,' he replied, reaching into his coat pocket. Mortified, he discovered that the ticket was missing. / “你的车票呢，先生？”收票员戈兹曼向一位年轻的乘客招了招手。“啊，对了。我的票就在这里，”他一边回答，一边伸手进外套口袋里了。当他发现车票不知所踪时，顿时石化了。\"/playMusic none/globalFade/viewport -100 -100/pause 1000/warp Sebastian -1000 -1000/warp Sam -1000 -1000/warp Abigail -1000 -1000/warp Jodi -1000 -1000/warp Robin -1000 -1000/warp Demetrius -1000 -1000/warp Shane -1000 -1000/warp Maru -1000 -1000/warp Pierre -1000 -1000/warp Caroline -1000 -1000/viewport 14 11 true/pause 1000/speak Elliott \"...'Clara, there's something I must tell you,' he blurted as she turned to leave. Clara turned, slowly, and saw the look of desperation in Horatio's eye. At that moment Gozman burst into the compartment, red-faced. / “克莱拉，有件事我必须告诉你，“看见她转身离开，他不禁脱口而出。克莱拉慢慢转过身子，看见霍雷肖眼中的绝望。同一时间，愤怒的戈兹曼冲进了厢房。\"/stopAnimation Elliott/showFrame Elliott 34/pause 800/speak Elliott \"Well, that concludes my reading. I'll be selling signed copies of the book by the front desk. Thanks for listening!$h / 阅读就到此为止。我会在前台出售亲笔签名版的书本。谢谢收听$h\"/faceDirection Lewis 3/faceDirection Marnie 1/faceDirection Emily 2 true/faceDirection Clint 1/move Elliott 0 4 3/faceDirection farmer 1/pause 600/speak Elliott \"Well, how was it? / 感觉怎么样？\"/emote farmer 32/speak Elliott \"Thanks. $h / 谢谢。$h#$b#You know, I got the idea for writing a romance novel from you. Do you remember? / 其实我创造科幻小说的灵感是来自于你的。你还记得吗？#$b#That's why I've dedicated this book to you...$l / 所以我把这本书献给你……$l\"/move Elliott -1 0 3/emote Elliott 32/pause 1000/end"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Events/Backwoods",
      "When": {
