      "Entries": {
        "6963327/f Abigail 3500/O Abigail/t 610 1700": "continue/-100 -100/farmer 39 14 0 golem 37 15 0 Abigail -100 23 0/addWorldState golemGrave/makeInvisible 37 11 5 7/skippable/pause 1000/viewport 39 11 clamp true/move farmer 0 -3 0/doAction 39 10/pause 500/doAction 39 10/pause 1000/move farmer 1 0 0/playMusic none/pause 100/doAction 39 10/playSound rockGolemSpawn/move Golem 0 -4 0/doAction 39 10/move Golem 2 0 1/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 3/pause 300/playSound rockGolemHit/pause 100/faceDirection farmer 2 true/animate farmer false true 100 94/jump farmer/pause 700/showFrame Golem 5/specificTemporarySprite swordswipe 39 11/playSound swordswipe/pause 250/playSound hitEnemy/startJittering/positionOffset farmer 8 0/pause 20/positionOffset farmer 8 0/pause 20/positionOffset farmer 8 0/pause 20/positionOffset farmer 8 0/pause 20/positionOffset farmer 8 0/pause 20/positionOffset farmer 8 0/pause 20/positionOffset farmer 8 0/pause 20/positionOffset farmer 8 0/playSound clubhit/stopJittering/pause 20/showFrame Golem 4/showFrame farmer 5/pause 1000/move Golem 1 0 1/warp Abigail 49 14/animate Golem false true 150 4 5 6 7/move Abigail -5 0 3/jump Abigail/animate Abigail false true 100 32/speak Abigail \"*gasp*...!$7 / 嘶呼……！$7\"/stopAnimation Abigail/speed Abigail 8/move Abigail -5 0 0/speed Abigail 8/move Abigail 0 -3 1/pause 250/animate Abigail false false 200 50 51/specificTemporarySprite swordswipe 39 11/playSound swordswipe/pause 250/playSound rockGolemHit/stopAnimation Golem/shake Golem 250/faceDirection Golem 3 true/pause 500/animate Abigail false false 200 50 51/specificTemporarySprite swordswipe 39 11/playSound swordswipe/pause 250/playSound rockGolemHit/stopAnimation Golem/shake Golem 250/pause 250/animate Abigail false false 200 50 51/specificTemporarySprite swordswipe 39 11/playSound swordswipe/pause 250/playSound rockGolemDie/specificTemporarySprite golemDie/warp Golem -100 -100/pause 750/playMusic echos/speed Abigail 4/move Abigail 1 0 1/pause 700/animate Abigail false true 100 39/pause 100/emote Abigail 28/pause 400/speak Abigail \"@...?$6 / @……？$6\"/pause 1000/speak Abigail \"@... are you okay?$6 / @……你没事吧？$6\"/pause 1500/startJittering/pause 500/stopJittering/pause 1000/startJittering/pause 500/stopJittering/pause 1000/stopAnimation farmer/showFrame farmer 0/jump farmer/pause 250/stopAnimation Abigail/showFrame Abigail 4/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 3/speak Abigail \"It looks like you're just scraped up a little... you had me worried! / 看起来只是有一些擦伤……你可让我担心坏了！\"/pause 450/animate Abigail true true 100 33/positionOffset Abigail 8 0/positionOffset farmer -8 0/animate farmer true true 100 101/pause 1500/positionOffset farmer 8 0/positionOffset Abigail -8 0/stopAnimation farmer/stopAnimation Abigail/showFrame Abigail 4/pause 1300/faceDirection Abigail 2/pause 800/move Abigail 0 1 2/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 500/move farmer 0 1 3/emote Abigail 28/pause 1200/speak Abigail \"I... I've never taken a life before...$s / 我……我之前从来没有杀过活物……$s\"/pause 700/faceDirection Abigail 1/pause 550/quickQuestion #It's sad, but there was no other option.#Monsters don't deserve our sympathy!#It's a harsh world, kid.#Did you have to kill him?(break)speak Abigail \"Yeah... I did what I had to do.$s / 是啊……我做了该做的事。$s#$b#I guess the world's a pretty tough place. It was either you or him, right?$6 / 我想世界是非常残酷的。不论是对你来说，还是对他来说……$6\"(break)speak Abigail \"...Aren't they just trying to survive, like us?$s#$b#They may be our enemies, but I still think they deserve sympathy.$6#$b#Still... I did what had to be done.$6\"(break)speak Abigail \"Huh? That's pretty funny coming from someone who just got rescued...$h#$b#But... yeah... Sometimes reality forces us to do things we'd rather not... Guess I'm learning that the hard way.$6\"(break)speak Abigail \"Hey! I saved your life, didn't I? Maybe you should think about that instead of putting me on a guilt trip.$a\"\\pause 600/pause 500/emote Abigail 40/pause 500/speak Abigail \"Look... You've gotta be more careful from now on. I don't want to lose you. / 从现在起，你必须更加小心。我不想失去你。\"/pause 500/animate Abigail true true 100 33/positionOffset Abigail 8 0/positionOffset farmer -8 0/animate farmer true true 100 101/specificTemporarySprite heart 40 11/pause 2000/positionOffset farmer 8 0/positionOffset Abigail -8 0/stopAnimation farmer/stopAnimation Abigail/showFrame Abigail 4/pause 1300/faceDirection Abigail 2/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 500/animate Abigail false true 100 0 1 2 3/positionOffset Abigail 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Abigail 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Abigail 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Abigail 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Abigail 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Abigail 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Abigail 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Abigail 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Abigail 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Abigail 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Abigail 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Abigail 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Abigail 0 2/pause 50/stopAnimation Abigail/pause 500/showFrame Abigail 26/pause 100/showFrame Abigail 27/pause 600/speak Abigail \"Let's put him to rest nearby... okay?$6 / 我们找个安静的地方把它埋掉吧……$6\"/pause 600/fade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 1000/playSound dirtyHit/pause 600/playSound dirtyHit/pause 600/playSound dirtyHit/pause 600/playSound dirtyHit/pause 2000/end dialogue Abigail \"Good thing I brought my sword today!$6\""
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Events/BathHouse_Pool",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "pennyHeartbroken": "move Penny 0 -2 0/faceDirection farmer 0/shake Penny 5000/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/stopSwimming farmer/stopSwimming Penny/end warpOut",
        "38/f Penny 2500/t 1900 2400/n pennySpa": "echos/-1000 -1000/farmer 13 23 2 Penny 9 29 1/swimming farmer/swimming Penny/skippable/showFrame Penny 31/viewport 13 27 true/pause 2000/playSound slosh/move farmer 0 6 3/positionOffset farmer 0 16/pause 700/speak Penny \"There you are... I was worried you didn't get my note.$6 / 你来了……我还担心你没收到我的字条呢。$6\"/playSound slosh/move Penny 1 0 1/pause 1500/faceDirection Penny 0/speak Penny \"It looks like we're alone.$8 / 看来只有我们在这里。$8\"/pause 800/speak Penny \"The water feels so good after being out in the cold of night, doesn't it?$6 / 这里的水感觉真清凉，对吧？$6\"/faceDirection farmer 0/pause 1300/faceDirection Penny 1/pause 500/playSound slosh/move Penny 1 0 1/faceDirection farmer 3/speak Penny \"$q -1 null#Do you know why I asked you here tonight?$8 / 你知道我今晚约你出来的原因吗？$8#$r -1 0 event_pool1#You have something to tell me. / 你有话想对我说。#$r -1 0 event_pool2#I'm not exactly sure. / 我不大清楚。#$r -1 0 event_pool3#You wanted to see me in my bathing suit. / 你想见穿着泳装的我。\"/faceDirection Penny 3/pause 800/faceDirection Penny 1/speak Penny \"Um, how do I say this...$8 / 呃，该怎么说呢……$8\"/pause 1000/playSound slosh/move Penny 1 0 1/pause 500/speak Penny \"I've been meaning to tell you for a while now... about how I feel.$8 / 我有句话想对你说很久了……是有关我的感受的。$8#$b#I can't stop thinking about you...$8 / 我总是不由自主地想着你……$8#$b#I've never felt this way about anyone.$8 / 我从未对任何人有过这种感觉。$8\"/speak Penny \"$q -1 null#...$8 / ……$8#$r -1 0 event_pool4#I feel the same way about you. / 我对你也有同样的感受。#$r -1 -1500 event_pool5#Sorry, but I don't like you in that way... / 抱歉，但是我对你没有这种感觉……\"/fork pennyHeartbroken/pause 1000/showFrame Penny 32/pause 200/playSound slosh/positionOffset Penny 2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 2 0/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 2 0/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 50/eyes 1 -10000/positionOffset Penny 2 0/positionOffset farmer -2 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 2 0/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 2 0/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 2 0/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 2 0/positionOffset farmer -2 0/specificTemporarySprite heart 13 29/pause 1200/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 2000/stopSwimming farmer/stopSwimming Penny/end warpOut"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Events/Beach",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "20/f Alex 500/z winter/p Alex/w sunny": "playful/-100 -100/farmer 27 7 2 Alex 25 17 2/showFrame Alex 23/skippable/animate Alex false true 125 16 17 18 19 20 21 22 23 23 23 23 23 23 23 23 23 23 23 23/viewport 28 14 true/move farmer 0 10 2/stopAnimation Alex/showFrame Alex 24/pause 600/showFrame Alex 23/speak Alex \"Oh, hi. / 嗨。\"/pause 300/emote Alex 40/speak Alex \"Um, it's @, right? / 呃，你是@，对吧？\"/pause 800/faceDirection farmer 3/pause 800/faceDirection farmer 2/speak Alex \"I'm just enjoying this great weather, @. / 我只是在享受这天气，@。\"/pause 1000/faceDirection Alex 1/pause 500/showFrame Alex 24/speak Alex \"Hmm...$u / 嗯……$u#$b#Hey, go long!$h / 喂，要试玩一下不！$h\"/pause 500/move farmer 2 0 3/pause 1000/showFrame Alex 4/animate Alex false false 80 24 25 25 26 4/pause 240/playSound throw/animate farmer true true 100 30/specificTemporarySprite joshFootball/null/pause 500/stopAnimation farmer/pause 700/speak Alex \"Heh... Nice try. / 呵……接得漂亮。\"/pause 500/move farmer -2 0 2/pause 800/faceDirection Alex 2/speak Alex \"I'm going to be the first professional gridball player from Stardew Valley... There's no doubt in my mind. / 我将会成为星露谷的第一位专业格球选手……我毫不怀疑。#$b#I already led my school's team to the regional playoffs... Now I'm just training and getting stronger so I can claim my spot on the roster of the Zuzu City Tunnelers. You just wait! / 我已经率领校队打入了区域季后赛……现在我只需一直训练加强自己以便获得加入祖祖城隧道队主力队的机会。你等着瞧吧！\"/pause 1000/question fork1 \"#I believe in you!#Wow, you're really arrogant. / #我相信你！#哇，你真够自大的。\"/fork arrogantJosh/faceDirection Alex 1/pause 500/speak Alex \"Thanks, @. I'll remember that. / 非常感谢，@。我会记住的。\"/move Alex 1 0 1/pause 500/end dialogue Alex \"Hey, that was fun, huh?\"",
        "29/f Sebastian 2000/t 1200 2300/w rainy": "rain/12 38/farmer 12 29 2 Sebastian 12 39 2/skippable/move farmer 0 7 2/faceDirection Sebastian 0/pause 400/speak Sebastian \"@? / @？\"/pause 500/move farmer 0 2 2/speak Sebastian \"Hey. I'm surprised to find you out here in the rain. / 嘿，没想到会在雨中遇见你。\"/pause 500/faceDirection Sebastian 2/pause 200/move farmer 1 0 2/move farmer 0 1 3/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 1000/playMusic echos/pause 1000/speak Sebastian \"Look at those dark clouds looming over the horizon... / 你看天边那些乌云……\"/pause 2000/speak Sebastian \"I hope they come this way. / 希望是奔我们而来的。\"/faceDirection farmer 3/pause 800/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 1000/speak Sebastian \"I like this weather because it makes everyone disappear... you know? / 我喜欢这种天气，所有人都消失不见……#$b#Being around people makes me feel anxious.$s / 因为人一多我就感到紧张。$s\"/faceDirection Sebastian 1/pause 400/faceDirection Sebastian 2/pause 400/speak Sebastian \"I don't feel that way around you, though.$7 / 不过跟你在一起我没有紧张的感觉。$7\"/pause 2000/emote Sebastian 28/speak Sebastian \"We're getting soaked... / 我们都成落汤鸡了……\"/pause 900/showFrame Sebastian 39/animate Sebastian false false 300 37 38 39/pause 300/playSound cast/pause 280/specificTemporarySprite umbrella/pause 800/speak Sebastian \"Here... There's room for two.$7 / 来……这里有足够两人的位置。$7\"/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 3/animate farmer true true 100 6 7/playSound dwop/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 100/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 100/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 100/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 100/stopAnimation farmer/pause 800/faceDirection farmer 3/animate farmer true true 100 6 7/playSound dwop/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 100/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 100/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 100/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 100/stopAnimation farmer/pause 800/faceDirection farmer 3/animate farmer true true 100 6 7/playSound dwop/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 100/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 100/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 100/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 100/stopAnimation farmer/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 3500/end",
        "13/f Haley 1500/z winter/t 1000 1600": "desolate/35 11/farmer 35 3 2 Haley 35 11 2/speed Haley 4/skippable/move Haley -2 0 3/pause 300/faceDirection Haley 2/move Haley 4 0 1/pause 300/faceDirection Haley 0/move Haley -2 0 2/emote Haley 28/move farmer 0 5 2/faceDirection Haley 0/emote Haley 16/speak Haley \"@! Come here, quick!$s / @！快来！$s\"/move farmer 0 2 2/speak Haley \"My bracelet is gone! I know I had it on when I got here... $s / 我的手镯不见了！我来这里的时候还戴着的……$s#$b#But now it's gone and I can't find it anywhere...$s / 但现在消失了，找来找去都找不到……$s\"/emote farmer 16/faceDirection farmer 3/faceDirection farmer 1/faceDirection farmer 2/emote farmer 8/speak Haley \"$q 48 null#I'll never find another one like it...$s / 这东西现在已经买不到了……$s#$r 48 -30 Event_beach1#Relax, I'll just buy you a new one! / 别担心，我给你买个新的！ #$r 48 50 Event_beach2#I'm really sorry... / 太遗憾了……\"/faceDirection Haley 2/move farmer 1 0 2/move farmer 0 1 3/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 600/showFrame Haley 22/pause 500/speak Haley \"Sorry, Great-Grandma. I lost your precious bracelet. Please forgive me.$s / 对不起，曾祖母。我弄丢了你珍贵的手镯。请原谅我。$s\"/playMusic ocean/pause 1000/message \"Could she have dropped it nearby? / 会不会是掉在附近了？\"/playerControl haleyBeach/globalFade .015/viewport -1000 -1000/warp farmer 36 11/faceDirection farmer 3/positionOffset farmer 0 16/faceDirection Haley 1/pause 500/viewport 35 11 true/pause 800/playMusic sadpiano/speak Haley \"Is that...?$8 / 那个是……？$8\"/emote Haley 16/jump Haley/pause 600/speak Haley \"You found it!$h / 你找到了！$h\"/showFrame Haley 23/positionOffset Haley 2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Haley 2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Haley 2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Haley 2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Haley 2 1/pause 50/positionOffset Haley 2 1/pause 50/positionOffset Haley 2 1/pause 50/eyes 5 -5000/positionOffset Haley 2 1/pause 50/positionOffset Haley 2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Haley 2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Haley 2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Haley 2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Haley 2 0/pause 50/speak Haley \"Thank you so much, @. You're a lifesaver. / 太感谢你了，@。你真是我的恩人。\"/eyes 1 -5000/pause 3000/speak Haley \"I won't forget what you did for me here.$l / 我不会忘记你的帮忙的。$l\"/end dialogue Haley \"I really owe you one, @.\"",
        "arrogantJosh": "pause 500/faceDirection Alex 3/emote Alex 12/faceDirection Alex 2/speak Alex \"Hmmph... I think someone's a little jealous.$a / 嗯……有人嫉妒了。$a\"/move Alex 0 -15 0 true/speak Alex \"I'm out of here.$a / 我先走了。$a\"/faceDirection farmer 0/end dialogue Alex \"...$a\"",
        "733330/f Sam 750/w sunny/t 700 1500/z winter/y 1": "ocean/-1000 -1000/farmer 40 9 2 Sam 41 18 2 Vincent 43 22 2/skippable/animate Vincent false true 500 18 19/specificTemporarySprite beachStuff/viewport 42 19 true/move farmer 0 9 1/faceDirection Sam 3/speak Sam \"Hello @. Nice day, isn't it? / 嗨，@。天气不错吧？\"/faceDirection farmer 2/faceDirection Sam 2/pause 800/speak Sam \"I'm just keeping an eye on my little brother. It's good for him to get some fresh air on a day like this. / 我只是来看看我弟弟。这种天气带他出来玩玩挺不错的。\"/pause 1700/speak Sam \"Our Dad used to take us to the beach on sunny days like this.$h / 我们父亲也常常在风和日丽时带我们去沙滩玩。$h\"/jump Vincent/stopAnimation Vincent/showFrame Vincent 0/pause 1000/move Vincent 0 -4 3/move Vincent -1 0 3/faceDirection Sam 1/faceDirection farmer 1/playMusic desolate/speak Vincent \"Sam...?$u / 山姆……？$u\"/pause 900/speak Vincent \"Is Dad ever going to come home?$s / 父亲还会回来吗？$s\"/emote Sam 28/showFrame Sam 34/pause 800/speak Sam \"Of course, Vince. Dad's going to come back as soon as he possibly can.$7 / 那是当然的，文森特。父亲一做好他的事就会尽快赶回来的。$7\"/pause 600/speak Vincent \"But I heard some grown-ups saying that... that all of our troops are getting shot to pieces.$s / 但是我听到很多大人说……我们的部队被打得落花流水。$s\"/showFrame Sam 35/pause 1500/speak Sam \"Don't believe everything you hear!$8 / 不要相信谣言。$8\"/showFrame Sam 4/speak Sam \"Don't you remember how strong Dad is? He'd never let a pathetic Gotoro grunt get him like that! Don't you worry!$a / 你忘了父亲有多强大吗？他才不会让垃圾戈特洛士兵抓到！你别担心！$a#$b#And always remember that Mom and I are here to play with you if you ever feel lonely. / 而且别忘了还有妈妈和我在这里陪你玩。\"/playMusic ocean/speak Vincent \"Okay! / 好的！\"/jump Vincent/pause 1000/move Vincent 1 0 2/showFrame Sam 4 true/faceDirection Sam 2 true/move Vincent 0 4 2/animate Vincent false true 500 18 19/playSound sandyStep/pause 800/faceDirection Sam 3/pause 800/faceDirection Sam 2/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 1000/speak Sam \"To be honest, I have no idea if my old man will come back... We've all read the reports. Our soldiers are falling by the thousands.$s / 老实说，我都不知道父亲会不会回来……新闻都播报了。我们的士兵伤亡惨重。$s#$b#But what am I going to say to Vincent?$7 / 但我又怎么能告诉文森特这些事呢？$7\"/pause 1000/question null \"#It's best to be honest with kids.#You did the right thing. Kids should have hope. / #对小孩子坦白很重要。#你做得很对。不能让小孩子失去希望。\"/emote Sam 40/pause 1000/splitSpeak Sam \"You think so?$7#$b#Maybe you're right... The world is a cruel place, but kids have to learn that one way or another.$s~Yeah... kids should play and have fun while they still have the chance.\"/pause 700/faceDirection Sam 3/faceDirection farmer 1/speak Sam \"Hey did I tell you the band's starting to come together? / 对了，我有告诉你乐队开始打出名堂了吗？#$b#Yeah! It turns out Abigail's a pretty good drummer. And Sebastian seemed to really want her in the band...$h / 对！阿比盖尔是个很棒的鼓手。而塞巴斯蒂安非常重视她……$h\"/pause 500/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/end",
        "288847/f Alex 2000/p Alex/w sunny/G !IS_PASSIVE_FESTIVAL_TODAY SquidFest": "ocean/-100 -100/farmer 52 13 2 Alex 53 24 2/showFrame Alex 38/skippable/viewport 53 24 true/pause 2000/speak Alex \"*sniff*...$s / *吸气*……$s\"/move farmer 0 11 2/pause 1000/showFrame Alex 36/pause 500/showFrame Alex 37/pause 500/speak Alex \"Oh... @. You saw me crying.$s / 哦……@。被你看见我流泪了。$s\"/pause 500/showFrame Alex 36/pause 1000/showFrame 95/pause 2000/speak Alex \"It was today, twelve years ago... that my Mom died.$9 / 十二年前的今天……我母亲离开了人间。$9\"/pause 1000/speak Alex \"I still remember her well... she'd make salted radish sandwiches for lunch... and toss the gridball with me in the back yard.$9 / 我很想念她……她经常做腌萝卜三明治给我们当午餐……经常跟我在后院玩格球。$9#$b#She took good care of me... and I was too young to really say 'thanks'. Now she's gone forever.$9 / 她把我照顾得很好……年轻时不懂得如何说“谢谢”。现在却子欲养而亲不待。$9\"/pause 1000/showFrame Alex 38/pause 1000/speak Alex \"This is the only keepsake I have left... her secret music box.$s / 这是我保存下来的唯一信物…………她的秘密音乐盒。$s\"/pause 1000/playSound openBox/showFrame Alex 35/pause 500/playMusic tinymusicbox/pause 10000/specificTemporarySprite JoshMom/pause 20000/playMusic ocean/pause 900/showFrame Alex 37/pause 900/showFrame Alex 36/pause 800/speak Alex \"$q -1 null#So... What are you thinking right now, @?$9 / 那么……你现在在想什么，@？$9#$r -1 0 event_box1#Honor your mother's memory by always doing your best. / 活出精彩人生以报答你母亲养育之恩。#$r -1 0 event_box2#You shouldn't dwell in the past. / 你不应该沉浸在过去不放手。#$r -1 0 event_box3#I'll always be here for you if you get lonely. / 要是你寂寞了，我永远会陪伴你。#$r -1 0 event_box4#Get over it. Life is hard for everyone. / 咬咬牙撑过去。人生不易，且行且珍惜。\"/pause 1000/showFrame Alex 36/pause 1000/speak Alex \"Well, there's no sense sitting around sniveling... let's head back to town.$9 / 呆在这里发呆也不算事……咱们回镇子去吧。$9\"/showFrame Alex 0/stopAnimation farmer/move Alex 0 -2 0 true/move farmer 0 -2 0 false/pause 1000/faceDirection Alex 3/pause 800/speak Alex \"Um... @?$9 / 呃……@？$9\"/pause 800/faceDirection farmer 1/pause 500/speak Alex \"Don't tell anyone I was crying. Okay?$7 / 别告诉任何人我哭了，好吗？$7\"/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 2/animate farmer false true 100 102 103/pause 100/jump Alex/pause 1500/stopAnimation farmer/move farmer 0 -8 0 true/faceDirection Alex 0/emote Alex 16/speak Alex \"Hey!$7 / 嘿！$7\"/move Alex 0 -8 0 true/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/end",
        "NoToElliott": "emote Elliott 16/pause 800/faceDirection Elliott 1/showFrame Elliott 31/pause 1000/emote Elliott 28/pause 600/speak Elliott \"I see.$7 / 明白了。$7\"/move farmer 0 -10 0 true/pause 800/end dialogue Elliott \"...$a\"",
        "739330/t 600 1710/*n spring_2_1": "ocean/-1000 -1000/farmer 28 35 1 Willy 44 35 1/removeQuest 13/addMailReceived NOQUEST_13/skippable/animate Willy false true 250 28 29 30 31/viewport 44 35 true/move farmer 7 0 1/playSound seagulls/move farmer 7 0 1/pause 500/playSound seagulls/pause 1000/playSound seagulls/speak Willy \"Ahoy there, son.$u / 喂，孩子。$u^Ahoy there, miss.$u / 喂，姑娘。$u#$b#Heard there was a newcomer in town... Good to finally meet ya.$u / 听说镇子上搬来了一位新来的……终于见到你了。$u\"/pause 500/playSound seagulls/pause 1000/stopAnimation Willy/playSound dwop/faceDirection Willy 2 true/pause 50/faceDirection Willy 3/pause 1000/speak Willy \"Ah... I'm still tryin' to unwind from a month out on the salty seas...$h / 啊…………我还在放松自己，之前出海了整整一个月……$h#$b#It was a big haul! I sold a lot of good fish. / 那次真是场大丰收啊！我卖了很多鱼。#$b#Finally saved enough to buy me a new rod.$h / 终于存够钱购买一支新的鱼竿。$h\"/move Willy -1 0 3/pause 1000/speak Willy \"Here, I want you to have my old fishing rod.$h / 给，这条旧鱼竿就送给你好了。$h#$b#It's important to me that the art o' fishing stays alive. And hey, maybe you'll buy somethin' from the shop once in a while.$h / 最重要的是让钓鱼的传统流传下去。也许培养起你的兴趣后，你会光顾我的商店也说不定。$h\"/pause 1000/playSound seagulls/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 2/itemAboveHead rod/pause 3300/awardFestivalPrize rod/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 1000/playSound seagulls/move Willy 0 1 2/pause 1000/showFrame Willy 24/pause 1000/speak Willy \"There's good water here in the valley. All kinds o' fish. / 这里的水不错。有着各种各样的鱼。\"/pause 1000/faceDirection Willy 3/speak Willy \"Oh yeah. My shop's back open now, so come by if you need supplies.$h / 啊对了。我的店子恢复营业了，有需要的话随时来找我。$h#$b#I'll also buy anything you catch. / 你捕到什么也可以卖给我。#$b#'If it smells, it sells'. Heh heh. That's what my ol' Pappy used to say, anyway.$h / “能吃的，就能卖”。呵呵。反正我老爸经常这么说的。$h\"/pause 500/playSound seagulls/pause 500/move farmer 0 1 2/pause 1000/pause 500/animate Willy false true 250 28 29 30 31/viewport move 1 0 5500/pause 1500/playSound seagulls/pause 1500/playSound seagulls/pause 2000/end position 42 36",
        "7771191/t 2000 2500/f Krobus 3500/w sunny": "moonlightJellies/-1000 -1000/farmer 0 0 2 Krobus 84 40 2/showFrame Krobus 17/addTemporaryActor SeaMonsterKrobus 32 32 -1 -1 0 false/addLantern 735 83 40 1/positionOffset Krobus 0 52/viewport 84 40 clamp true/pause 3300/animate Krobus false true 500 17 18 17 19/specificTemporarySprite krobusBeach/pause 8000/stopAnimation Krobus/showFrame Krobus 17/pause 2000/emote Krobus 20/pause 4000/faceDirection SeaMonsterKrobus 0/playSound pullItemFromWater/animate SeaMonsterKrobus false false 100 20 21 22 23/warp SeaMonsterKrobus 84 45/pause 600/showFrame Krobus 0/jump Krobus/pause 100/animate SeaMonsterKrobus false true 250 8 9 10 11/pause 800/pause 1500/stopAnimation SeaMonsterKrobus/move SeaMonsterKrobus 0 -3 0/pause 1000/emote Krobus 8/pause 2000/animate SeaMonsterKrobus false false 100 16 17 18 19 19 19 19 19 19 19 19/playSound waterSlosh/pause 400/showFrame SeaMonsterKrobus 19/pause 500/playSound coin/warp Krobus -1 -1/faceDirection SeaMonsterKrobus 2 true/animate SeaMonsterKrobus false true 500 0 1/pause 2000/stopAnimation SeaMonsterKrobus/playSound waterSlosh/move SeaMonsterKrobus 0 3 2/animate SeaMonsterKrobus false true 500 2 3/pause 3000/stopAnimation SeaMonsterKrobus/playSound waterSlosh/move SeaMonsterKrobus 3 0 1/playSound waterSlosh/move SeaMonsterKrobus -6 0 3/emote SeaMonsterKrobus 20 true/playSound waterSlosh/move SeaMonsterKrobus 6 0 1/playSound waterSlosh/move SeaMonsterKrobus -9 0 3 true/pause 2000/fade/viewport -2000 -2000/pause 3000/end",
        "711130/t 600 1710/f Willy 1500": "ocean/30 34/farmer 27 35 1 Willy 30 34 2 Gus -10 -10 0/skippable/addConversationTopic willyCrabs/showFrame Willy 24/move farmer 3 0 0/showFrame Willy 0/pause 800/speak Willy \"Ah... it's a good thing you turned up, lad. / 啊……太好了，你出现了，小伙子。^Ah... It's a good thing you turned up, miss. / 啊……啊……太好了，你出现了，小姐。#$b#I've got a... a bit of a problem I could use a hand with... / 我遇到……遇到一点麻烦，可能需要帮忙……\"/faceDirection Willy 3/faceDirection Willy 0/pause 1000/faceDirection Willy 3 true/pause 100/faceDirection Willy 2/speak Willy \"Er... It'd be best if I just showed ya... / 呃……还是直接让你看一下比较好……\"/pause 600/faceDirection Willy 3 true/pause 100/faceDirection Willy 0/speak Willy \"Take a deep breath, now. / 现在深呼吸一次。\"/pause 300/playSound doorClose/warp Willy -100 -100/move farmer 0 -1 0/pause 500/playSound doorClose/warp farmer -100 -100/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/changeLocation FishShop/specificTemporarySprite willyCrabExperiment/warp Willy 5 7/faceDirection Willy 0/playMusic ragtime/pause 500/viewport 5 7 true/pause 5000/warp farmer 5 9/playSound doorClose/pause 100/jump farmer/pause 1000/emote farmer 16/faceDirection Willy 3 true/pause 100/faceDirection Willy 2/speak Willy \"As you can see... / 正如你能看到……#$b#And smell... heh... / 能闻到……呃……#$b#The old girls 'ran wild' last night... heh...$h / 这是老姑娘们昨晚的“狂欢”……呵……$h#$b#My experiment needs a little work... / 我的实验需要一些投入……\"/move farmer 0 -1 0/move farmer 2 0 1/emote farmer 56/warp Gus 5 9/playSound doorClose/pause 100/jump Gus/pause 1000/speak Gus \"Hooo~... Back at it again, huh Willy?$h / Hooo~……又在做实验，威利？$h\"/textAboveHead Willy \"Aye... / 对……\"/move Gus 0 -1 3/move Gus -2 0 3/pause 1000/speak Gus \"They look fresh all right... / 它看起来很新鲜……\"/faceDirection Willy 3/speak Willy \"Aye... These are the finest, meatiest crabs you'll ever set yer eyes on.$h / 对……这些是你从未见过的最美味、最肥美的螃蟹。$h#$b#They be a little too feisty, though...$s / 但是，他们有点过于活跃了……$s\"/pause 1000/emote Gus 40/pause 500/jump Gus/pause 1000/speak Gus \"I'll take the whole lot!$h / 我全要！$h#$b#With a discount for the extra labor, of course... / 当然，额外的人工要打点折……\"/pause 2000/move farmer 1 0 0 true/move Gus -1 0 0 false/move farmer 0 -1 0 true/move Gus 0 -1 0 false/faceDirection Willy 0/pause 1000/playSound slimeHit/specificTemporarySprite removeSprite 3/pause 1000/playSound slimeHit/specificTemporarySprite removeSprite 1/pause 1000/playSound fishSlap/specificTemporarySprite removeSprite 2/pause 500/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 1500/speak Gus \"Looks like we got 'em all... / 似乎全归我们了……\"/pause 1000/speak Willy \"Goodbye, me sweet ladies...$s / 再见，甜心美人们……$s\"/pause 1000/speak Gus \"Psst... @... Don't tell Willy, but I'll be doing a special on crab cakes at the saloon for the next few days... / 嘘……@……不要告诉威利，但我会在接下来的几天里在酒吧中做点特别的蟹肉饼……\"/pause 1000/end position 30 34",
        "3131209/n willyBugWadCutscene": "ocean/-2000 -2000/farmer 49 22 2/addTemporaryActor Willy 16 64 52 26 2/addCraftingRecipe Quality Bobber/skippable/specificTemporarySprite WillyWad/animate Willy false true 500 8 9 10 11/pause 1000/speak Willy \"Hehe... they love it... Look at 'em go!$h / 嘿嘿……它们很喜欢……看它们动来动去！$h\"/pause 1000/playSound slosh/pause 500/playSound slosh/pause 500/playSound slosh/pause 500/viewport 52 24 true/pause 1000/move farmer 0 2 2/textAboveHead Willy \"Ahoy! / 啊嘿！\"/pause 2000/speak Willy \"I was just thinkin' of you, lad. / 我正想到你，小伙子。^I was just thinkin' of you, miss. / 我正想到你，小姑娘。#$b#This bug meat you found is perfect! / 你找到的虫肉真是完美！#$b#Hehe... When I said 'fresh', I didn't expect it to still be wrigglin'! / 哈哈……我说“新鲜”，不是想要还在蠕动的！#$b#But I'm not complaining! The fish love it...  Hehehe...$h / 啊，我没在抱怨！鱼儿很喜欢……哈哈哈……$h\"/emote farmer 28 true/pause 300/playSound slimeHit/pause 500/playSound slimeHit/pause 500/playSound slimeHit/pause 1000/speak Willy \"As a way of saying 'thanks', I wanted to teach you an old fisherman's secret... My ol' Pappy taught me this on a fishing trip many years ago. / 作为感谢，我想教给你一个老渔夫的秘密……我老爹好多年前带我出去钓鱼的时候教我的。\"/pause 500/playSound reward/message \"Learned how to craft 'Quality Bobber' / 已学会制作“优质浮标”\"/pause 500/speak Willy \"Using that bobber will attract higher quality fish. / 用那个浮标可以吸引来高品质的鱼。#$b#That means more money in yer pocket, ${lad^lass}$. Hehe...$h / 然后口袋里就会有更多的钱，${小伙子^小姑娘}$。哈哈……$h\"/pause 1500/pause 300/playSound fishBite/pause 500/pause 400/playSound FishHit/animate Willy false true 100 17 18/textAboveHead Willy \"Got one! / 钓到了！\"/shake Willy 5000/pause 200/playSound slosh/pause 200/playSound slosh/pause 220/playSound slosh/pause 160/playSound slosh/pause 200/playSound slosh/pause 220/playSound slosh/pause 160/playSound slosh/pause 200/playSound slosh/pause 220/playSound slosh/pause 160/playSound slosh/pause 200/fade/viewport -1000 -1000/end",
        "43/f Elliott 2500/w sunny/t 700 1300/G !IS_PASSIVE_FESTIVAL_TODAY SquidFest": "ocean/-1000 -1000/farmer 13 16 2 Elliott 13 27 1/specificTemporarySprite elliottBoat/skippable/viewport 17 26 clamp true/move farmer 0 8 2/faceDirection Elliott 0/speak Elliott \"Hey. / 嘿，\"/move farmer 0 2 2/faceDirection Elliott 1/faceDirection farmer 1/speak Elliott \"Look... I fixed up that old rowboat that's been sitting by my house. Pretty nice, huh? / 话说……我修好了我屋子旁边那艘旧划艇。厉害吧？\"/pause 500/faceDirection Elliott 0/pause 500/speak Elliott \"@... Would you do me the honor of joining me for her maiden voyage?$l / @……不知道你是否愿意加入它的首航？$l\"/faceDirection farmer 2/question fork1 \"Get in the boat?#Yes#No / 是否登上划艇？#是#不是\"/fork NoToElliott/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/changeToTemporaryMap ElliottSea false/playSound wateringCan/pause 1000/playSound wateringCan/playMusic 50s/warp farmer 26 20/positionOffset farmer 0 8/warp Elliott 26 20/showFrame Elliott 25/positionOffset Elliott 0 60/viewport 25 20 true/pause 5000/speak Elliott \"So my book's been out for a while now... It's not a best-seller or anything, but it's been getting some good reviews from the critics. / 我出的书上市一阵子了……虽然销量不算好，但是却获得了专家们的好评。#$b#And I really couldn't have finished it without your moral support.$l / 要不是你的支持和鼓励，我肯定无法完成我的书。$l\"/pause 1000/speak Elliott \"Actually, that's not true at all. I would've finished it either way.$h / 其实，我是在开玩笑的。就算没有你我自己也能完成这本书。$h#$b#But I am grateful that you believed in me... in my vision. And, well... / 不过我很感激你信任我……和我的梦想。还有，那个……\"/pause 500/speak Elliott \"Um... @? How do I say this...$8 / 呃……@？该怎么说呢……$8\"/emote Elliott 40/speak Elliott \"Well, we've been friends for a while now... But I'm... I'm not sure if I feel that way about you anymore.$l / 我们成为朋友一阵子了……但是我……我不确定自己是否还当你是朋友。$l\"/emote farmer 16/speak Elliott \"No! I'm not saying I want to cut all ties with you!$8 / 不是！我不是想要跟你断绝关系的意思！$8#$b#In fact... quite the opposite.$l / 事实上……恰恰相反。$l\"/pause 1000/emote Elliott 40/pause 500/speak Elliott \"...Let's see, how do I put this...?$l / 让我想想，我该怎么说才对……？$l#$b#For once, I'm at a loss for words... / 晕，我竟然什么都说不出口了……\"/playMusic elliottPiano/pause 2500/showFrame Elliott 35/screenFlash 1/warp Elliott 26 20/positionOffset Elliott 24 8/positionOffset farmer -20 16/faceDirection farmer 1 true/showFrame 101/specificTemporarySprite heart 26 20/playSound dwop/pause 1500/startJittering/pause 700/speak Elliott \"$q -1 null#@? You're trembling...$l / @？你在颤抖……$l#$r -1 50 event_boat1#I'm happy. / 我很开心。#$r -1 -50 event_boat2#You're making me very uncomfortable. Stop. / 你让我整个人都不好了。别这样。\"/stopJittering/fork tooBold/pause 1800/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/speak Elliott \"We'd better head back before the southern wind picks up.$l / 我们还是趁刮起南风前回去吧。$l^Uh oh... The vibration from your body has caught the attention of a Crimsonfish... We'd better get out of here.$l / 啊……你刚才的颤抖引来了绯红鱼的注意……我们得马上离开了。$l\"/pause 1400/speak Elliott \"Look at the valley from here... it finally looks like 'Home'. / 从这里远眺山谷……终于有一种“家”的感觉了。\"/pause 4000/speak Elliott \"*sigh*... What a day...$l / *唉*……真是累人的一天……$l\"/end"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Events/BoatTunnel",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "9348571/Hl willyBoatFixed": "ocean/6 8/farmer -1000 -1000 0 Willy -1000 -1000 0/skippable/pause 4000/warp farmer 6 12/playSound doorClose/move farmer 0 -2 0/emote farmer 8/pause 1500/warp Willy 6 12/playSound doorClose/move Willy 0 -1 0/pause 500/emote Willy 28/pause 250/move farmer 1 0 0/move Willy 0 -1 0/pause 700/speak Willy \"Aye... a sad sight, isn't she? / 唉……看起来让人挺伤感，是吧？\"/pause 500/speak Willy \"She was me father's boat... Served him well for over 50 years. / 是我父亲的船……陪他度过了 50 多年。#$b#But now she can barely stay afloat.$s / 不过现在连浮在水面上都很吃力。$s\"/faceDirection Willy 1/faceDirection farmer 3/speak Willy \"I'd repair her myself, but I don't have the right materials, ${lad^miss}$. / 我想亲自去修，但是没有合适的材料，${小伙子^小姑娘}$。\"/faceDirection Willy 0/speak Willy \"Aye... 200 pieces of hardwood to patch the hull would be a good start. / 是……我们先要 200 块硬木用来把船体修补好。#$b#But we'll also need to get the ticket machine back up, and the iridium anchor repaired. / 不过之后还得修好售票机，还有铱锚。\"/faceDirection farmer 0/pause 400/speak Willy \"If I could get me hands on the right materials, and repair the ol' girl... well, then I could take you to the Fern Islands. / 如果你能帮我找来合适的材料，让我好修理这艘船……嗯，那我就可以带你去芬群岛。\"/faceDirection Willy 1/faceDirection farmer 3/speak Willy \"Volcanic islands full of strange parrots, they say... / 据说有火山岛屿，上面有好多奇怪的鹦鹉……\"/pause 400/quickQuestion #I'd like to help#Nah, I'll pass...(break)emote Willy 32\\speak Willy \"Aye... I thought you would, ${lad^miss}$.$h / 好嘞……我知道你会帮忙的，${小伙子^小姑娘}$。$h\"\\speak Willy \"I'll leave this door unlocked for ya... you can come drop off the materials whenever you like.\"(break)emote Willy 28\\speak Willy \"Alright, suit yourself...$s#$b#If you have a change of heart, you can always come back and help out. I'll leave this door unlocked, anyhow.\"/pause 2000/end"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Events/BusStop",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "9581348/e 2128292/t 1600 1800": "continue/-1000 -1000/farmer 22 19 0 Shane 23 10 2 Alex 22 13 0 Gus 19 11 1 Pam 20 10 2/viewport 22 11 clamp true/skippable/move farmer 0 -4 0 true/move Alex 0 -4 0 true/proceedPosition Alex/playSound thudStep/warp Alex -100 -100/move farmer 0 -1 0/move Shane 0 1 2/speak Shane \"Hey, there you are!$6 / 嘿，你来了啊！$6#$b#I'm glad you decided to come. We should get going...$6 / 我非常开心你能过来。我们该动身了……$6\"/move Pam 2 0 0/move Pam 0 -1 0/warp Pam -100 -100/playSound thudStep/move Gus 3 0 0/move Gus 0 -2 0/faceDirection Shane 3 true/playSound thudStep/warp Gus -100 -100/move farmer 0 -4 0 true/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/playMusic none/pause 800/playSound busDriveOff/pause 4000/changeToTemporaryMap Stadium false/speak Shane \"We're almost there... / 我们快到了……\"/pause 1500/playSound glug/pause 500/speak Shane \"*gulp* ...pre-game nerves...$10 / 嗝……比赛前总感到紧张不安……$10\"/pause 1000/playMusic Stadium_ambient/warp farmer 19 19/faceDirection farmer 2/positionOffset farmer 0 16/warp Alex 14 12/faceDirection Alex 2/warp Gus 30 14/faceDirection Gus 2/warp Shane 22 12/pause 3000/advancedMove Shane false 0 7 -2 0/viewport 22 18 clamp true/proceedPosition Shane/faceDirection Shane 2/speak Shane \"Here, I got you another cold one... / 来，我帮你带了一瓶冷饮……\"/showFrame Shane 25/pause 1000/playSound coin/showFrame 90/showFrame Shane 0/pause 2000/farmerEat 184/pause 1000/animate Shane false true 200 20 20 20 20 20 20 20 20 20 20 21 22 23 24 24 24 24 23 22 21 20 20 20 20/pause 6000/animate Shane false true 400 0 30 0 30 0 31 0 31/pause 1000/faceDirection farmer 1/pause 1000/speak Shane \"Hey, I've been meaning to say... $6 / 嗨，我是想说……$6#$b#Thanks for sticking with me through everything... my anxiety, depression... you know...$6 / 谢谢你陪我一起度过这一切…你懂的…我的焦虑和沮丧。$6#$b#You've been a really good friend to me.$6 / 你让我意识到你对我来说真的很重要。$6\"/pause 2000/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 4000/speak Shane \"Anyway...  it's your first gridball game, huh? / 话说，这是你第一次看格球比赛吧？\"/pause 1000/speak Shane \"$q -1 null#Well, what do you think? / 好吧, 你想什么呢？#$r -1 10 event_stadium1#Noisy... It makes me appreciate how peaceful it is back home. / 这让我意识到家里是多么地让人感到安逸。#$r -1 10 event_stadium2#Fun... Pelican Town seems really boring in comparison. / 相比之下，鹈鹕镇让人感到很无聊。\"/stopAnimation Shane/pause 100/jump Shane/showFrame Shane 18/pause 1000/speak Shane \"Gahh!! Look, the Tunnelers are on the attack!$10 / 啊！看，隧道队在进攻！$10\"/showFrame Shane 0/pause 1500/playSound Stadium_cheer/pause 500/showFrame Shane 31/jump Shane/textAboveHead Shane \"Goal!! / 入球了！\"/jump Alex/jump Gus/pause 100/textAboveHead Alex \"Goal! / 入球了！\"/pause 2000/jump Shane/pause 2000/showFrame Shane 34/positionOffset Shane -2 0/pause 10/positionOffset Shane -2 0/pause 10/positionOffset Shane -2 0/pause 10/positionOffset Shane -2 0/pause 10/positionOffset Shane -2 0/pause 10/positionOffset Shane -2 0/pause 10/positionOffset Shane -2 0/pause 10/positionOffset Shane -2 0/pause 10/positionOffset Shane -2 0/pause 10/positionOffset Shane -2 0/pause 10/showFrame farmer 94/pause 800/showFrame farmer 0/pause 800/faceDirection farmer 1 true/animate farmer false true 100 101/pause 1000/pause 2000/stopAnimation farmer/showFrame Shane 12/positionOffset Shane 2 0/pause 10/positionOffset Shane 2 0/pause 10/positionOffset Shane 2 0/pause 10/positionOffset Shane 2 0/pause 1500/faceDirection Shane 1/speak Shane \"Oh!...$10 / 哦！……$10\"/move Shane 1 0 1/speak Shane \"Um... Sorry... I got carried away there.$10 / 嗯……对不起……我最好离你远点。$10#$b#Maybe I had one too many... / 我怕我会克制不住自己……\"/pause 3000/faceDirection Shane 3/pause 800/move farmer 2 0 1/pause 1000/animate farmer false true 100 101/positionOffset farmer 2 0/pause 10/positionOffset farmer 2 0/pause 10/positionOffset farmer 2 0/pause 10/positionOffset farmer 2 0/pause 10/showFrame Shane 18/pause 800/showFrame Shane 0/pause 800/showFrame Shane 34/specificTemporarySprite heart 22 18/pause 3000/viewport move -1 -1 5000/pause 3000/globalFade/viewport -2000 -2000/pause 3000/playMusic none/pause 1000/speak Shane \"Well... that was definitely a good game.$l / 嗯……真是场精彩的比赛。$l\"/pause 2000/speak Shane \"Oh, yeah... and we won, too.$l / 噢，耶……而且我们也赢了。$l\"/pause 1000/pause 1000/speak Shane \"Well... see you soon.$6 / 好吧，下次见。$6\"/pause 2000/end",
        "520702/a 11 23 11 24/t 600 1600/z spring/z fall/z summer": "winter_day_ambient/-1000 -1000/farmer 10 23 1 Krobus 26 23 3/viewport 24 23 clamp true/addQuest 31/skippable/move Krobus -2 0 3/pause 1000/emote Krobus 16/jump Krobus/pause 500/speed Krobus 8/move Krobus 20 0 1 true/move farmer 2 0 1 true/move false/playSound shadowpeep/warp Krobus -1000 -1000/pause 500/emote farmer 8/pause 1000/end",
        "4081148/e 47/t 1600 1900": "none/-1000 -1000/farmer 23 22 0 Sam 24 10 2 Sebastian 25 11 3 Emily 20 11 3 Maru 19 10 2 Shane 22 15 0 Elliott 27 14 1 Leah 28 14 3 Abigail 23 11 1 Penny 28 10 3 Harvey 18 11 1 Linus 31 5 2 Jodi 18 15 2 Vincent 18 16 0/viewport 22 11 clamp true/skippable/move farmer 0 -10 0 true/move Shane 0 -6 0 true/proceedPosition Shane/warp Shane -100 -100/proceedPosition farmer/move farmer 1 0 0 false/speak Sam \"Hi @. Thanks for coming. / 嗨，@。你来啦。\"/faceDirection Sam 3/faceDirection Sam 1/faceDirection Sam 2/speak Sam \"Well, our gear's loaded already... Looks like everything's set. / 嗯，我们已经整装待发……一切都进展顺利。\"/jump Sam/pause 800/speak Sam \"Alright, everyone... let's get in the bus!$u / 那好，所有人注意……上车吧！$u\"/pause 600/move Abigail -1 0 0 true/move Emily 1 0 1 true/faceDirection Maru 1/proceedPosition Abigail/move Abigail 0 -2 2 true/move Sebastian -3 0 0 true/move Elliott -5 0 0 true/move Leah -5 0 0 true/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 3000/speak Sam \"*gulp*... I'm starting to get really nervous.$8 / *深呼吸*……我有点开始紧张了。$8\"/pause 1000/playSound busDoorOpen/pause 4000/speak Sam \"Okay, here we are... wish me luck!$u / 好的，我们到了……祝我好运吧！$u\"/pause 800/changeToTemporaryMap SamShow false/warp Sam 18 14/faceDirection Sam 0 true/warp Sebastian 21 14/positionOffset Sebastian 20 -20/warp Abigail 15 13/positionOffset Abigail 40 -24/warp farmer 18 20/warp Elliott 20 19/faceDirection Elliott 0/warp Leah 21 19/faceDirection Leah 0 true/warp Maru 13 16/faceDirection Maru 1 true/warp Harvey 14 17/faceDirection Harvey 0 true/warp Emily 21 16/faceDirection Emily 0 true/warp Shane 16 20/warp Linus 31 14/faceDirection Linus 0 true/warp Penny 17 16/faceDirection Penny 0 true/faceDirection Sebastian 2 true/warp Jodi 11 19/warp Vincent 12 19/faceDirection Jodi 0/viewport 18 15 true/move farmer 0 -4 0/pause 3000/faceDirection Sam 2/pause 800/jump Sam/pause 1000/cutscene bandFork/mail afterSamShow/end dialogue Sam \"Hey. The show was a great success! Thanks again, @.\"",
        "60367/u 0": "none/-1000 -1000/farmer 22 10 2 Robin 22 13 0 Lewis -100 -100 2/skippable/pause 500/playSound busDoorOpen/pause 5000/viewport 23 10 clamp true/move farmer 0 2 2/playMusic SettlingIn/speak Robin \"Hello! You must be @. / 你好！你就是@吧。#$b#I'm Robin, the local carpenter. Mayor Lewis sent me here to fetch you and show you the way to your new home. He's there right now, tidying things up for your arrival. / 我叫罗宾，是这里的木匠。是镇长刘易斯派我来送你去你的新家的。他本人已经在那里为你打扫屋子了。#$b#The farm's right over here, if you'll follow me. / 农场就在那边，跟我来吧。\"/viewport move 0 2 800/move Robin 0 5 2 true/pause 800/move farmer 0 4 2 true/fade/speed farmer 2/viewport -200 -200/changeLocation Farm/halt/warp Robin 78 17/faceDirection Robin 3/warp farmer 79 17/faceDirection farmer 3/viewport 70 16 clamp/viewport move -1 0 4000/move Robin -8 0 3 farmer -8 0 3/pause 700/faceDirection Robin 2/speak Robin \"This is %farm farm. / 这里就是%farm农场。\"/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 2/showFrame 94/jump farmer/startJittering/pause 1000/emote farmer 28/showFrame 0/stopJittering/pause 800/faceDirection Robin 1/pause 200/speak Robin \"What's the matter? / 怎么了？#$b#Sure, it's a bit overgrown, but there's some good soil underneath that mess! / 虽说是长满了杂草，但是下面的泥土可是很肥沃的！#$b#With a little dedication you'll have it cleaned up in no time. / 只要有点耐心，肯定很快就能清理干净它的。\"/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 3/pause 200/move Robin -7 0 0 farmer -7 0 0/pause 400/faceDirection Robin 0/speak Robin \"...And here we are, your new home.$h / ……铛铛铛铛，这就是你的新房子了。$h\"/pause 300/faceDirection farmer 0/pause 500/playSound doorClose/warp Lewis 64 15/pause 1500/speak Lewis \"Ah, the new farmer!$h / 啊，新来的农夫到了！$h\"/move Lewis 0 1 2/move Lewis 1 0 2/move Lewis 0 1 3/faceDirection farmer 1/faceDirection Robin 1/pause 600/speak Lewis \"Welcome! I'm Lewis, Mayor of Pelican Town. / 欢迎！我叫刘易斯，是星露谷的镇长。#$b#You know, everyone's been asking about you. / 你不知道，很多人都对你很好奇。#$b#It's not every day that someone new moves in. It's quite a big deal! / 因为这里很少有人搬进来的，所以你瞬间成了大家的关注对象！\"/pause 1000/faceDirection Lewis 3/pause 100/faceDirection Lewis 0/pause 500/speak Lewis \"So... You're moving into your grandfather's old cottage. / 那么……你是搬来你祖父的老房子。#$b#It's a good house... very 'rustic'. / 那是间很好的屋子……很有“乡土味”。\"/pause 300/faceDirection Robin 0 true/faceDirection farmer 0/viewport move 0 -1 2000/pause 3000/speak Robin \"Rustic? That's one way to put it... $4 / 乡土味？真是个糟糕的形容词……$4#$b#'Crusty' might be a little more apt, though.$4 / “顽固”还差不多。$4\"/faceDirection Lewis 3 true/jump Lewis/shake Lewis 1600/textAboveHead Lewis \"Rude! / 太无礼了！\"/showFrame Lewis 24/pause 500/faceDirection Robin 1 true/pause 100/faceDirection Robin 2 true/pause 100/animate Robin false true 100 32 33/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 1000/showFrame Lewis 12/stopAnimation Robin/pause 300/faceDirection Robin 1/showFrame Lewis 12/faceDirection farmer 1/speak Lewis \"Don't listen to her, @. She's just trying to make you dissatisfied so that you buy one of her house upgrades.$u / 别听她说的，@。她只是想诱惑你购买她的房屋升级服务。$u\"/showFrame Lewis 12/showFrame Robin 19/shake Robin 800/pause 1200/showFrame Robin 0/pause 600/animate Robin false true 300 34 35/textAboveHead Robin \"Hmmph. / 嗯。\"/pause 1500/speak Lewis \"Anyway... You must be tired from the long journey. You should get some rest. / 话说……你赶了那么远的路一定很累了。你该去休息下了。#$b#Tomorrow you ought to explore the town a bit and introduce yourself. / 明天你得到镇上走走认识些人。#$b#The townspeople would appreciate that. / 镇民们都很想认识你。\"/move Lewis 4 0 1 true/viewport move 1 0 2000/pause 3000/proceedPosition Lewis/faceDirection Lewis 0/pause 500/faceDirection Lewis 3/speak Lewis \"Oh, I almost forgot. If you have anything to sell, just place it in this box here. I'll come by during the night to collect it. / 哦，差点忘了。如果你有想出售的东西，放在这个盒子里就行。我每晚都会过来收走。#$b#Well... Good luck! / 那么……祝你好运！\"/pause 300/move Lewis 8 0 1 true/faceDirection farmer 0/stopAnimation Robin/advancedMove Robin false 0 1 2 0 0 -1 5 0/pause 1000/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/playMusic none/pause 2000/playSound rooster/pause 1000/end beginGame"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Events/CommunityCenter",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "Punch": "pause 100/move George 0 -3 3 true/showFrame Morris 12/textAboveHead Morris \"Hah! / 哈！\"/pause 500/speak Morris \"This means nothing. I'll just run a 75%-off sale and all my customers will come crawling back to me, begging for forgiveness. You'll see!$h / 这都是没有用的。只要我打个二五折，所有顾客都会回头来求我。你等着瞧吧！$h\"/shake Pierre 500/pause 1000/move George -5 0 3 true/speak Pierre \"No... Not this time, Morris.$u / 不……这次不会了，莫里斯。$u#$b#I think it's time we settled this once and for all.$u / 我们是时候把这件事彻底解决一下了。$u\"/pause 500/speak Morris \"Oh? And how do you propose we do that?$u / 哦？那你说我们该怎么办呢？$u\"/playMusic event1/pause 2000/animate Pierre false true 200 20 21/positionOffset Pierre 8 8/pause 1500/speak Morris \"Hah! Primitive... / 哈！真原始……\"/move Morris 0 1 2/speak Pierre \"If you're too scared to fight me then bring one of your co-workers! Or are all Joja employees such cowards?$u / 如果你被我吓破了胆的话，那就带个同事来吧！还是说 JOJA 的员工都这么胆小？$u\"/faceDirection Morris 1 true/pause 50/faceDirection Morris 0/shake Morris 1000/pause 1500/speak Morris \"Insult me all you like... but don't you DARE slander the good name of Joja!$u / 随便你怎么侮辱我……但不许你污蔑 Joja 的名字！$u\"/speed Morris 4/move Morris 0 -1 3/showFrame Morris 20/positionOffset Morris -4 -4/animate Morris false true 200 20 21/pause 2000/stopAnimation Morris/showFrame Morris 22/playSound clubhit/stopAnimation Pierre/showFrame Pierre 22/pause 500/jump Caroline/textAboveHead Caroline \"Pierre! / 皮埃尔！\"/speed Caroline 4/move Caroline 0 4 1 true/animate Morris false true 200 20 21/animate Pierre false true 200 20 21/pause 1000/jump Robin/showFrame Robin 19/textAboveHead George \"Ha! Good stuff! / 哈！好东西啊！\"/pause 1000/jump Lewis/stopAnimation Morris/showFrame Morris 22/playSound clubhit/shake Pierre 200/stopAnimation Pierre/showFrame Pierre 22/pause 500/animate Morris false true 200 20 21/animate Pierre false true 200 20 21/pause 2000/stopAnimation Morris/showFrame Morris 22/playSound clubhit/shake Pierre 200/stopAnimation Pierre/showFrame Pierre 22/pause 500/jump Caroline/speak Morris \"You're even weaker than your fresh produce selection!$u / 你的实力还不如你选择新鲜果蔬的眼光呢！$u\"/animate Morris false true 200 20 21/animate Pierre false true 200 20 21/pause 2000/speak Pierre \"And the way you throw punches is just like Joja...$u / 而你打架的能力就跟 Joja 的产品一样……$u#$b#Quantity over quality! / 重数量不重质量！\"/pause 1000/stopAnimation Morris/showFrame Morris 22/playSound clubhit/shake Pierre 200/stopAnimation Pierre/showFrame Pierre 22/pause 500/animate Morris false true 200 20 21/animate Pierre false true 200 20 21/pause 1000/pause 500/textAboveHead George \"Get him! / 收拾他！\"/pause 2000/stopAnimation Pierre/stopAnimation Morris/showFrame Pierre 17/showFrame Morris 20/pause 100/showFrame Pierre 18/showFrame Morris 23/playSound clubhit/shake Morris 250/pause 50/showFrame Pierre 17/showFrame Morris 20/pause 1000/showFrame Morris 20/pause 100/showFrame Pierre 18/showFrame Morris 23/playSound clubhit/shake Morris 250/pause 50/showFrame Morris 20/showFrame Pierre 17/pause 1000/showFrame Morris 20/pause 100/showFrame Pierre 18/showFrame Morris 23/playSound clubhit/shake Morris 250/pause 50/showFrame Morris 20/showFrame Pierre 17/pause 1000/shake Pierre 1000/showFrame Morris 19/pause 1000/showFrame Pierre 17/positionOffset Pierre 4 0/pause 100/positionOffset Pierre 4 0/showFrame Pierre 18/pause 100/positionOffset Pierre 4 0/showFrame Pierre 19/playSound clubSmash/warp Morris -2000 -2000/specificTemporarySprite morrisFlying/pause 2000/playSound barrelBreak/showFrame Pierre 4/pause 2000/move Pierre 1 0 0/pause 1000/playSound dwop/faceDirection Pierre 1 true/pause 50/faceDirection Pierre 2/pause 100/showFrame Pierre 23/playSound stoneStep/pause 500/globalFade/viewport -9999 -9999/pause 4000/message \"Morris and his JojaMart cronies were never heard from again. / 从此再没有人听到过莫里斯和他的 Joja 超市员工的消息。\"/pause 500/end position 52 20"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Events/DesertFestival",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "PlayerKilled": "none/-100 -100/farmer -2000 -2000 2/pause 1000/showItemsLost/pause 200/end"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Events/ElliottHouse",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "howLong": "pause 500/resetVariable/speak Elliott \"Oh, I'm not sure... I've been dabbling in piano since I was a kid.$7 / 噢，我也不确定……我从小就弹钢琴了。$7#$b#I'm not very good, but it's fun. / 我不算太好，但我很开心。\"/switchEvent elliottPianoJoin",
        "39/f Elliott 500/p Elliott": "50s/2 5/farmer 3 9 0 Elliott 1 5 0/skippable/move farmer 0 -1 0/pause 400/faceDirection Elliott 2/emote Elliott 16/speak Elliott \"@! Come in. / @！请进。\"/pause 500/move farmer 0 -2 3/move farmer -2 0 0/pause 500/speak Elliott \"Welcome to my humble... well, shack. / 欢迎光临寒……舍。\"/faceDirection Elliott 0/speak Elliott \"This is my writing desk. It's where I spend most of my time. / 这是我的书桌。我大部分时间都花在这上面。\"/pause 500/faceDirection Elliott 2/speak Elliott \"For as long as I can remember, I've wanted to be a writer. Have I told you that? / 从我懂事起，我就想当作家了。我跟你说过没？#$b#That's why I live out here by myself. I figured a lonely life by the sea would help me focus on my literary aspirations...$s / 所以我才自己住在这里。我发现独自住在海边有助于文学灵感的诞生……$s\"/faceDirection Elliott 1/speak Elliott \"Everyone back home said I was nuts... that I could never make it as a writer. / 家里人都说我疯了……说我永远都不可能当上作家。#$b#Can you believe it? They said 'For every successful author there's 1000 who fail miserably'. Such pessimism... it's sickening. / 你相信吗？他们说“每个成功作家的背后都有 1000 个悲惨的失败者”。多悲观呐……真让人难受。\"/pause 700/faceDirection Elliott 2/speak Elliott \"I can see it in your eyes... you believe in me, @. You've got that spark. / 我从你眼睛里就能看出来……你相信我，@。你眼中有热情。#$b#Now that's inspiring! That's what I'm looking for... / 真是太好了！这就是我想要的……\"/pause 500/emote Elliott 16/speak Elliott \"$q 958699 null#A question... What kind of books do you like, @? / 问个问题……你喜欢什么样的书，@？#$r 958699 30 event_idea1#Mystery / 悬念#$r 958700 30 event_idea2#Romance / 浪漫#$r 958701 30 event_idea3#Sci-Fi / 科幻\"/pause 500/speak Elliott \"Well! Enough talk about me! / 好！说我说得够多了！\"/pause 400/emote Elliott 16/speak Elliott \"Hmm... you probably know a lot about plants, don't you? / 唔……你应该很了解植物吧？\"/pause 500/faceDirection Elliott 1/speak Elliott \"Would you mind taking a look at this rose, here? I'm afraid it's not doing so well.$7 / 你能不能看看这盆玫瑰？它好像有点蔫。$7\"/pause 400/move farmer 2 0 0/move farmer 0 -2 3/pause 400/animate farmer true true 100 35/pause 200/end dialogue Elliott \"Thanks for talking with me... I'll be thinking about what you said.\"",
        "elliottPianoJoin": "pause 800/showFrame Elliott 0/animate Elliott false true 220 0 1 2 3/playSound woodyStep/positionOffset Elliott 0 8/pause 120/positionOffset Elliott 0 8/pause 120/positionOffset Elliott 0 8/pause 120/positionOffset Elliott 0 8/pause 120/positionOffset Elliott 0 8/pause 120/positionOffset Elliott 0 8/stopAnimation Elliott/faceDirection Elliott 2/pause 500/move Elliott 1 0 1 true/faceDirection farmer 1/pause 1500/showFrame Elliott 31/pause 800/emote Elliott 28/pause 800/speak Elliott \"I've been working day and night to try and finish my book... It's been driving me insane, @.$s / 我夜以继日想要完成我的书……我都快疯了，@。$s\"/showFrame Elliott 4/pause 800/move Elliott -2 0 0/pause 800/speak Elliott \"An occasional tune is the only recreation I allow myself.$7 / 我唯一的消遣就只有随性弹首曲子。$7\"/pause 600/faceDirection Elliott 2/speak Elliott \"There's just too much work to do! And my bank account's starting to run dry.$7 / 工作实在太多了！而且我的存款也渐渐见底了。$7#$b#Sometimes I wish I could just throw it all away and become a farmer like you.$h / 有时候我真想抛弃一切，像你一样当个农夫。$h\"/pause 300/faceDirection farmer 0/question fork1 \"#It's just as hard to be a farmer, you know.#Come live on the farm, I could use the extra help. / #当农夫也一样艰难。#过来农场生活吧，我需要帮忙。\"/fork extraHelp/pause 500/emote Elliott 16/speak Elliott \"You're right... that was an insensitive thing to say.$8 / 你说得对……事不关己所以才会说这种话。$8\"/move Elliott 0 1 3/faceDirection farmer 1/speak Elliott \"What I meant is that I'd like to get away from this dark, musty prison and experience a little bit of real life... that's all.$s / 我的意思是想要逃离这阴暗潮湿的监牢，去享受一点真正的生活……仅此而已。$s\"/animate Elliott true true 100 31/pause 800/emote Elliott 28/pause 500/speak Elliott \"*sigh*... sorry I'm complaining like this. I just need someone to talk to now and then.$7 / *唉*……抱歉让你听我唠叨了，我时不时就得跟别人吐吐苦水。$7\"/pause 500/stopAnimation Elliott/showFrame Elliott 4/pause 600/faceDirection Elliott 3/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/end",
        "extraHelp": "pause 500/emote Elliott 16/speak Elliott \"Seriously?$8 / 真的吗？$8\"/faceDirection Elliott 1/pause 400/speak Elliott \"It sounds wonderful... but I can't give up on my novel. It's already half-way done.$7 / 可我的小说不能弃坑啊。都快写完一半了。$7\"/animate Elliott true true 100 31/pause 800/emote Elliott 28/pause 500/speak Elliott \"*sigh*... sorry I'm complaining like this. I just need someone to talk to now and then.$7 / *唉*……抱歉让你听我唠叨了。我时不时就得跟别人吐吐苦水。$7\"/pause 500/stopAnimation Elliott/showFrame Elliott 4/pause 600/faceDirection Elliott 3/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/end",
        "423502/f Elliott 1500/p Elliott": "elliottPiano/-200 -1000/farmer 3 9 0 Elliott 8 4 0/skippable/positionOffset Elliott 32 16/animate Elliott false true 400 25 26 26 27 27 26 26 25 26 27 27 26 26 25/pause 1000/viewport 8 4 true/pause 24000/stopAnimation Elliott/showFrame Elliott 24/move farmer 0 -3 0/move farmer 4 0 0/showFrame Elliott 28/pause 1000/speak Elliott \"Ah... I thought someone was there.$7 / 啊……我就感觉到有人在那儿。$7\"/pause 1000/showFrame Elliott 30/animate Elliott false false 200 28 29 30/playSound dwop/pause 1000/question fork1 \"#That was wonderful.#How long have you been playing? / #真的很棒。#你弹了多久？\"/fork howLong/pause 500/emote Elliott 32/speak Elliott \"Thank you. I'm not very good, but it's fun to play.$h / 谢谢。我琴技不算太好，但我很开心。$h\"/switchEvent elliottPianoJoin"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Events/Farm",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "1590166/m 1000/t 600 930/d Mon Tue Thu Sat Sun/w sunny/h cat/H": "continue/64 15/farmer 64 15 2 Marnie 65 16 0 pet 63 16 2/skippable/faceDirection PetActor 2/pause 500/animate PetActor false false 120 16 17 18 18/pause 480/animate PetActor false true 120 18/pause 2000/speak Marnie \"Hello @!$h / 嗨，@！$h#$b#You see this cat here? / 你看见这只猫了吗？\"/faceDirection Marnie 3/pause 400/showFrame PetActor 18/playPetSound cat/pause 1200/faceDirection Marnie 0/speak Marnie \"I found it sitting outside the entrance to your farm! I think it's a stray... poor little thing.$s / 我看到它坐在你的农场门口！它可能是无家可归了……可怜的小东西。$s\"/showFrame PetActor 19/pause 500/showFrame PetActor 18/playPetSound cat/shake PetActor 150/pause 1500/speak Marnie \"I think it likes this place! Hey, um.... Don't you think this farm could use a good cat?$h / 它可能是喜欢这里！唔……你不觉得这个农场需要养只好猫吗？$h\"/catQuestion/pause 1000/faceDirection Marnie 3/speak Marnie \"Well, little %pet... You be a good kitty now... okay? / 哦，小宠物 %pet……现在你是只好猫咪了……知道吗？\"/pause 500/showFrame PetActor 19/shake PetActor 100/playPetSound cat/pause 800/animate PetActor false false 120 20 21 22 23 21 22 23 21 22 23 21 22 23 21 22 23 21 22 23 21 22 23/pause 200/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/end",
        "5/e 3/v Abigail/t 600 800": "continue/64 15/farmer 64 16 2 Abigail 64 18 0/pause 1500/speak Abigail \"Hi. Um... I just wanted to say sorry for acting so weird yesterday. / 嗨。呃……我为昨天奇怪的举止道歉。#$b#You probably understand what happened...$l / 你也许已经明白发生什么了……$l#$b#Uh, okay...bye. / 呃，那好……再见。\"/pause 500/end",
        "2128292/e 3900074/t 600 630/f Shane 2500/D Shane": "continue/64 15/farmer 64 16 2 Shane 64 18 0/pause 1500/skippable/speak Shane \"Hey, @!$6 / 嗨，@！$6\"/pause 1000/speak Shane \"Uh... So I got two tickets to the Tunnelers game tonight.$6 / 呃……我得到了 2 张今晚的隧道工人游戏门票。$6\"/pause 2000/speak Shane \"If you want to come, meet me at the bus stop around 5pm.$6 / 如果你有兴趣，今天下午 5 点左右我们在巴士站碰面。$6\"/pause 1000/end",
        "980559/t 600 1130/w sunny/e 739330/j 27/!Skill Fishing 1": "spring_day_ambient/64 15/farmer 64 16 2 Willy 64 18 0/skippable/pause 1500/speak Willy \"Good morning, ${lad^miss}$! / ${小伙子^小姑娘}$，早上好！\"/pause 800/speak Willy \"Sorry to bother you so early, but, eh... I've noticed you haven't been fishing much. / 很抱歉这么早打扰你，那什么，呃……我发现你好像没怎么钓鱼。\"/pause 200/emote farmer 28/pause 200/speak Willy \"Aye... it can be difficult to get into the sport, for a beginner. / 嗐……初学者想上手钓鱼确实会有点难度。\"/pause 400/speak Willy \"So, I figured I'd give you a few pointers... maybe it'll help you develop yer sea legs! / 所以我想着来给你一点提示……或许能让你再熟悉熟悉！\"/pause 500/playMusic distantBanjo/pause 500/speak Willy \"So, you'll want to hold the rod like this, see?... / 好了，你要这样拿着鱼竿，明白吗？……\"/pause 300/fade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 1000/message \"Willy gave you a quick lesson on fishing basics. / 威利简单地教了你一些钓鱼基础知识。\"/gainSkill Fishing 1/pause 500/message \"You feel more confident already! / 你觉得信心满满！\"/pause 400/viewport 64 15 clamp true/pause 1000/speak Willy \"One more thing... I wanted to give you this. / 哦对了……我还要把这个给你。#$b#It's called a 'training rod'. It should make catching fish a lot easier. / 这个是“训练鱼竿”，用它钓鱼会容易很多。#$b#Just be aware that you'll only be able to catch basic fish with this. But it's a great way to develop your skills early on! / 不过用这个只能钓到基础鱼类，一开始的时候用来锻炼技术还是很好的！\"/pause 800/itemAboveHead (T)TrainingRod/pause 3300/awardFestivalPrize (T)TrainingRod/pause 200/pause 500/speak Willy \"I hope you'll give fishing another try. Once you get the hang of it, you'll be having a great time. / 希望你能再试试钓鱼，掌握窍门之后钓起来还是很开心的。#$b#Good luck out there!$h / 祝你好运！$h\"/pause 1000/end",
        "980558/t 600 1130/w sunny/f Gus 1250": "playful/64 15/farmer 64 16 2 Gus 64 18 0/skippable/pause 1500/speak Gus \"Good morning! / 早上好！\"/pause 500/faceDirection Gus 3/pause 600/speak Gus \"Ah... what a beautiful day, huh? / 啊……天气真好啊！\"/pause 400/faceDirection Gus 0/speak Gus \"You know, as the Saloon owner, I hear about everything that's going on in town. / 这个，我是餐吧老板，所以能听到镇上发生的所有事情。#$b#I remember when you first moved here... everyone was a bit unsure of what to expect. / 我还记得你刚来这里的时候……大家都对将来的事情有些忐忑。#$b#A stranger from the city... an unknown personality...$s / 一个从城里来的陌生人……未知的性格……$s\"/textAboveHead Gus \"One sec... / 等一下……\"/faceDirection Gus 2/animate Gus false true 250 24 25/pause 500/playSound slimeHit/pause 500/playSound slimeHit/pause 500/playSound slimeHit/pause 500/playSound slimeHit/pause 500/stopAnimation Gus/pause 500/faceDirection Gus 0/pause 500/speak Gus \"Sorry, I have to stir this pot every 5 minutes. / 不好意思，我得每隔 5 分钟给这个锅搅拌一次。\"/emote farmer 40/speak Gus \"Anyway, what was I saying? Oh yeah... you know, it's like when you're making a sauce... / 不管了，我刚说到哪了？哦，对……那啥，这就像你在制作酱汁的时候……\"/playMusic none/speak Gus \"...If you put in a new spice you could ruin everything!$s / ……如果你加入一种新的香料，就有可能把整个酱汁都毁了！$s\"/pause 500/playSound fireball/animate Gus false true 100 26/shake Gus 1000/specificTemporarySprite sauceFire/pause 2000/animate Gus false true 200 24 25/pause 400/playSound slimeHit/pause 400/playSound slimeHit/pause 400/playSound slimeHit/pause 400/playSound slimeHit/pause 400/playSound slimeHit/animate Gus false true 100 24/pause 500/playSound discoverMineral/specificTemporarySprite sauceGood/pause 800/playMusic distantBanjo/speak Gus \"...But then again, there's always a chance you'll create something new and delicious! Right? Hahahaha.$h / ……但话又说回来，如果你加入新的香料，也总是有可能创造出新的美味的，对吧？哈哈哈哈。$h\"/pause 100/stopAnimation Gus/faceDirection Gus 0/emote farmer 8/faceDirection Gus 3/faceDirection Gus 0/pause 500/speak Gus \"Er... What I'm trying to say is...$s / 呃……我想说的是……$s#$b#It's been great having you in town, and I've come to think of you as one of my good friends! / 你能来到镇上真是太好了，我已经把你当作我的好朋友了！\"/emote farmer 32/speak Gus \"Anyway, I came to give you something... / 总之，我是来给你件东西的……#$b#I was cleaning out the back room and I found this old Mini-Jukebox. I want you to have it! / 我在清理里屋的时候，找到了这个旧的迷你点唱机。希望你能收下它！\"/pause 800/itemAboveHead jukebox/playSound getNewSpecialItem/pause 3300/awardFestivalPrize jukebox/pause 200/message \"Received a 'Mini-Jukebox' / 收到一个“迷你点唱机”\"/pause 800/speak Gus \"It's actually an old Do-It-Yourself project of mine, from many years ago. They're pretty easy to make! / 这实际上是好几年前我自己手工做的。做起来还挺容易的！#$b#So, just in case you wanted to make more, I brought the blueprints for you... / 所以，我还给你带来了图纸，这样你就可以再做几个……\"/pause 200/playSound getNewSpecialItem/addCraftingRecipe Mini-Jukebox/pause 500/message \"Learned how to craft a 'Mini-Jukebox' / 已学会制作“迷你点唱机”\"/pause 800/speak Gus \"Well, I'm gonna head home. I gotta get this marinara back on the stove! Have a good one! / 好了，我该回家了。我得把这个红酱放回炉子上！祝你愉快！\"/pause 500/end",
        "3917587/f Alex 3500/O Alex/t 500 820/M 5000/d Sun/y 2": "continue/-10000 -1000/farmer -100 -100 2 Alex -100 -100 2/warp Alex -100 -100/warp farmer -100 -100/faceDirection Alex 2/viewport 64 15 clamp true/pause 2000/playSound doorClose/warp farmer 64 15/pause 500/move farmer 0 2 2/playSound doorClose/warp Alex 64 15/pause 300/faceDirection farmer 1 true/pause 100/faceDirection farmer 0/speak Alex \"Hey, @. Before you head out... / 嘿，@。在你出发之前……#$b#I hate to ask this... but can I have 5,000g? / 我很抱歉要问你……能分给我 5,000 金吗？#$b#It's for a secret project I'm working on... I know we have a joint bank account, but I thought I should ask anyway. / 我正在参与的一个秘密项目要用……我知道我们的银行账户是共用的，但我觉得还是该先问问你。\"/pause 1000/question fork0 \"Give Alex 5,000g for his secret project?#Yes#No / 要给亚历克斯 5,000 金参与他的秘密项目吗？#是#否\"/fork giveAlexMoney/playMusic none/pause 1000/emote Alex 12/speak Alex \"Really? You won't spare a measly 5,000g to make me happy?$a / 真的假的？你连 5,000 金这点小钱都不肯拿出来让我开心一下的吗？$a#$b#I didn't know you were such a cheapskate...$s / 你居然是这样的铁公鸡……$s\"/pause 500/faceDirection Alex 1 true/pause 100/faceDirection Alex 0/pause 500/emote Alex 28/pause 400/speak Alex \"I just wanted to have a little fun...$s / 我就是想找点乐子……$s\"/pause 800/playSound doorClose/warp Alex -100 -100/pause 2000/end dialogue Alex \"I don't want to talk to you right now...$s\"",
        "2146991/y 3/H": "spring_day_ambient/8 7/farmer 64 16 2/broadcastEvent/globalFade/viewport 8 7 clamp true/pause 3000/grandpaCandles/pause 3000/end",
        "91/f Marnie 750/t 600 930": "continue/64 15/farmer 64 16 2 Marnie 64 18 0/pause 1500/addQuest 21/skippable/speak Marnie \"Good morning, ${Mr.^Ms.}$ @!$h / 早上好啊，@${先生^小姐}$！$h#$b#I came by to ask you a favor, since you're such a kind neighbor. / 我来是请你帮忙的，因为你是个善良的邻居。#$b#You see, I'm trying to train my goats to say 'hello'... but they simply won't pay attention to me unless I have their favorite treat, cave carrots!$u / 我在训练我的山羊向人打招呼……但它们的注意力根本不在我身上，除非我用它们最爱的食物山洞胡萝卜来吸引它们！$u#$b#So... since I'm scared of the mines... I thought, well, maybe you would bring me a cave carrot when you have the chance? / 所以……由于我害怕矿山……你有机会的话能不能给我带一根山洞胡萝卜？#$b#There's no pressure... but if you want to, just swing by my house between 9:00 AM and 5:00 PM with a cave carrot. You'll make an old girl very happy. Bye. / 不强迫的……但如果你愿帮我的话，上午 9:00 到下午 5:00 之间带着山洞胡萝卜来我家就好。你的善举会让一位老姑娘非常开心的。再见。\"/pause 300/end dialogue Marnie \"My goats go wild over cave carrot... I can't imagine why.\"",
        "102/z spring/z summer/z fall/d Mon Tue Wed Thu Fri Sat/y 1/H": "continue/64 15/farmer 64 16 2 Pierre 64 18 0/broadcastEvent/skippable/pause 1500/speak Pierre \"Hello there, @. So! Your first year in Stardew Valley is almost over, huh? / 你好啊，@。那么！你在星露谷的第一年就要结束了吧？#$b#If you keep buying seeds from me, you'll be twice as productive next year!$h / 如果你继续从我这里买种子，我保证明年你的产量会翻一倍！$h#$b#And I have some exciting news... / 我还有一些振奋人心的消息……#$b#I'll be selling new seed varieties in my shop next year! I should have 1 new variety per season. / 我的店里明年还会卖新品种的种子！每一季度我就会推出 1 个新品种。#$b#...Well, that's all I wanted to say. Have a good one. / 我要说的就这么多。祝你愉快。\"/pause 300/move Pierre 0 1 2/pause 1000/faceDirection Pierre 0/speak Pierre \"You know... I wouldn't even bother trying my competitor's seeds.$u / 你知道吗……我根本不会操心去试用其他同行的种子。$u#$b# Pierre's seeds are the *highest* quality seeds you'll find anywhere. That's a promise.$h / 皮埃尔商店的种子绝对是最高档的。这我保证。$h\"/pause 500/end",
        "992559/t 600 1130/n clothFound/o Emily/w sunny": "continue/64 15/farmer 64 16 2 Emily 64 18 0/skippable/pause 1500/speak Emily \"Hi @! Good morning! / 嗨，@！早上好！\"/pause 500/faceDirection Emily 3/pause 800/faceDirection Emily 0/speak Emily \"You seem to be doing well... the farm looks great!$h / 看起来你干得不错……农场看起来很棒！$h\"/pause 500/emote farmer 32/pause 500/speak Emily \"So... you've been here a while, and I'm sure you've acquired some 'cloth' by now... right? / 那么……你来这里有一段时间了，你现在肯定有一些“布料”了……对吧？\"/pause 500/speak Emily \"Well, did you know that you can use cloth to tailor all kinds of clothes? All you need is access to a sewing machine... / 是这样，你知不知道可以用布来缝制各种衣服？你只需要一台缝纫机就可以了……#$b#And I happen to have one at home! Feel free to swing by and use it any time.$h / 正好我家里有一台！你可以随时到我家来用。$h\"/pause 800/playSound reward/message \"You can now access Emily's sewing machine! / 你现在可以使用艾米丽的缝纫机了！\"/pause 800/speak Emily \"To start tailoring, you'll need a piece of cloth and a secondary item. Experiment and see what unique styles are out there! / 你需要一块布料和一个辅助物品就可以开始缝衣了。试试看都有什么独特风格！\"/pause 500/emote Emily 32/pause 500/end",
        "66/e 295672/t 600 700/H": "continue/64 15/farmer 64 16 2 Gunther 64 18 0/broadcastEvent/rustyKey/skippable/pause 1500/speak Gunther \"Oh, good morning ${Mr.^Ms.}$ @! / 早上好啊，@${先生^小姐}$！#$b#I hope it's not too early...$s / 希望还不算太早……$s#$b#Well, I just wanted to stop by and thank you in person for all the wonderful artifacts and minerals you've discovered... you've done so much for one person!$h / 我只是想过来亲自说声谢谢，谢谢你发现的那些美丽的古物和矿物……都是靠一己之力实在太了不起了！$h#$b#In fact, I've just received a letter from the office of the regional secretary of artifacts... We're being honored with the coveted 'golden shovel' award for our significant contributions to the field! / 其实，我刚刚收到地区古物秘书寄来的一封信……我们因对地区做出杰出贡献，被授予“金铲子”奖！#$b#And it's all thanks to you!$h / 这都多亏了你！$h#$b#Well, I should let you get back to your work... / 唔，我不应该再耽误你工作了……\"/pause 500/faceDirection Gunther 2/pause 700/emote Gunther 16/faceDirection Gunther 0/speak Gunther \"Oh! I almost forgot! / 噢！我差点忘了。#$b#I have a gift for you... It's an old key that's been sealed in the museum vault for at least 100 years. It's a little rusty, but still beautiful.$h / 我有个礼物要给你……这是一把在博物馆金库封藏了至少 100 年的古老钥匙。虽然有点生锈了，但还是非常漂亮。$h\"/pause 500/pause 500/playSound reward/message \"You got the 'Rusty Key'! It's been added to your wallet. / 你获得了“生锈的钥匙”！已经添加到你的钱包。\"/pause 500/end",
        "992559/t 600 1130/n clothFound/O Emily/w sunny": "continue/64 15/farmer 64 16 2 Emily 64 18 0/skippable/pause 1500/speak Emily \"Good morning, @.$h / 早上好，@。$h\"/pause 500/speak Emily \"I just remembered... I have a sewing machine at my old place! / 我刚刚想起来……我老房子那里有一台缝纫机！\"/pause 500/speak Emily \"If you ever feel like making clothes, you should swing by and check it out.$h / 如果你想做衣服，可以过去看看。$h\"/pause 800/playSound reward/message \"You can now access Emily's sewing machine! / 你现在可以使用艾米丽的缝纫机了！\"/pause 800/speak Emily \"To start tailoring, you'll need a piece of cloth and a secondary item. Experiment and see what unique styles are out there! / 你需要一块布料和一个辅助物品就可以开始缝衣了。试试看都有什么独特风格！#$b#I'm going to have a lot of fun seeing you in all kinds of different outfits!$h / 如果你能穿上各式各样的服装，我会很开心的！$h\"/pause 500/emote Emily 20/pause 500/end",
        "690006/n slimeHutchBuilt/H": "continue/64 15/farmer 64 16 2 Marlon 66 15 2/broadcastEvent/skippable/pause 1000/move farmer -1 0 2/move farmer 0 1 1/pause 500/showFrame Marlon 12/pause 1000/speak Marlon \"Bumped into Robin this morning... she told me you've got a new Slime Hutch! / 今天早上碰到罗宾……她告诉我你建了一个新的史莱姆屋子！\"/showFrame Marlon 8/shake Marlon 1600/textAboveHead Marlon \"Not bad! / 不错嘛！\"/pause 1600/showFrame Marlon 12/pause 500/speak Marlon \"I was into slime breeding at your age. It's a great hobby... but dangerous. / 我像你这么大的时候也对史莱姆的繁衍很感兴趣。这个爱好很好……但也危险。#$b#How'd you think I lost this eye? / 你以为我是怎么丢掉这只眼睛的？\"/shake Marlon 1000/showFrame Marlon 12/textAboveHead Marlon \"Hah! / 哈！\"/pause 1000/textAboveHead Marlon \"Just Kidding. / 开玩笑的啦！\"/showFrame Marlon 12/pause 200/showFrame Marlon 7/animate Marlon false false 120 4 5 6 7/pause 800/speak Marlon \"Here, I've got something for you. / 我有东西要给你。\"/faceDirection farmer 2/itemAboveHead slimeEgg/pause 1000/pause 1000/pause 1300/awardFestivalPrize slimeEgg/pause 300/faceDirection farmer 1 true/pause 500/showFrame Marlon 12/speak Marlon \"It's a slime egg. You can place that inside a slime incubator to hatch it. / 这是史莱姆的蛋。你可以放在史莱姆孵化器里孵化它。#$b#Now, take a good hard look at that egg. Next time you're out slime-hunting keep your eyes peeled for more eggs. They're rare, but slimes do drop them from time to time. / 睁大眼睛好好看看这颗蛋吧。下次你出去找史莱姆的时候就可以简单地找更多的蛋了。它们的蛋虽然很稀有，但史莱姆也是需要繁衍的。#$b#Collect eggs from different slimes to add some variety to your herd! / 收集不同的史莱姆蛋来丰富所养史莱姆群落的种类！\"/pause 500/end",
        "897405/m 1000/t 600 930/d Mon Tue Thu Sat Sun/w sunny/h dog/H": "continue/64 15/farmer 64 15 2 Marnie 65 16 0 pet 63 16 2/skippable/faceDirection PetActor 1/pause 500/animate PetActor false false 120 20 21 22 23 23/pause 480/animate PetActor false true 120 23/pause 2000/speak Marnie \"Hello @!$h / 嗨，@！$h#$b#You see this dog here? / 你看见这只狗了吗？\"/faceDirection Marnie 3/pause 400/showFrame PetActor 26/playPetSound dog_bark/pause 200/showFrame PetActor 23/pause 600/showFrame PetActor 26/playPetSound dog_bark/pause 200/showFrame PetActor 23/pause 1000/animate PetActor false true 200 24 25/playPetSound dog_pant/pause 400/playPetSound dog_pant/pause 400/playPetSound dog_pant/pause 1200/faceDirection Marnie 0/speak Marnie \"I found it sitting outside the entrance to your farm! I think it's a stray... poor thing.$s / 我看到它坐在你的农场门口！它可能是无家可归了……可怜的小东西。$s\"/pause 500/animate PetActor false true 400 23 31/pause 1500/speak Marnie \"Hey, it seems to like this place! Hey, um.... Don't you think this farm could use a good dog?$h / 它可能是喜欢这里！唔……你不觉得这个农场需要养只好狗吗？$h\"/catQuestion/pause 1000/faceDirection Marnie 3/speak Marnie \"Well,  %pet... You be a good pooch now... okay? / 好吧，%pet……小宠物……现在你是只好狗狗了……知道吗？\"/pause 500/stopAnimation PetActor/showFrame PetActor 26/playPetSound dog_bark/pause 200/showFrame PetActor 23/pause 1000/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/end",
        "3911124/f Leah 3500/O Leah/t 500 820/w sunny/z winter/d Sun": "continue/-10000 -1000/farmer -100 -100 2 Leah -100 -100 2/warp Leah -100 -100/addConversationTopic leahPaint 0/warp farmer -100 -100/faceDirection Leah 2/viewport 64 15 clamp true/pause 2000/playSound doorClose/warp farmer 64 15/pause 500/move farmer 0 2 2/playSound doorClose/warp Leah 64 15/pause 300/faceDirection farmer 1 true/pause 100/faceDirection farmer 0/speak Leah \"Hey, @. I have an idea... / 嘿，@。我有个主意……#$b#I want you to meet me in Cindersap Forest tomorrow, at noon. / 我想要你明天中午在煤矿森林跟我碰头。#$b#I'm gonna teach you how to paint!$h / 我会教你怎么画画！$h\"/pause 1000/speak Leah \"If the weather's bad, we'll do it the next day. Okay? / 如果天气不好，我们就改到第二天。好吗？\"/emote farmer 32/end dialogue Leah \"It'll be nice to explore your creative side a bit more, don't you think?\"",
        "giveAlexMoney": "pause 200/addMailReceived gaveAlexMoney/money -5000/emote Alex 20/pause 500/speak Alex \"Great! Swing by the Saloon on Sunday and I'll show you the end result!$h / 太棒了！你星期天顺路来餐吧一趟，我给你看最终结果！$h\"/pause 500/end",
        "3917600/f Emily 3500/O Emily/t 500 820": "continue/-10000 -1000/farmer -100 -100 2 Emily -100 -100 2/warp Emily -100 -100/warp farmer -100 -100/faceDirection Emily 2/viewport 64 15 clamp true/pause 2000/playSound doorClose/warp farmer 64 15/pause 500/move farmer 0 2 2/playSound doorClose/warp Emily 64 15/pause 300/faceDirection farmer 1 true/pause 100/faceDirection farmer 0/speak Emily \"Hey, honey... before you get to work today, do you have a moment? / 嘿，亲爱的……在你今天去干活之前，能留给我一点时间吗？#$b#I've been working on something special for you... but I need a little help finishing it. / 我给你准备了一样特别的东西……但我需要一点帮助来完成。\"/move farmer 0 -1 0/speak Emily \"It's a secret, so I can't tell you what it is... but could you bring me 200 pieces of fiber? / 这是秘密，所以我不能把具体情况告诉你……你能给我弄来 200 份纤维吗？\"/addQuest 126/pause 500/speak Emily \"That's all I need! Just bring the 200 fiber by when you have a chance... no rush! / 我就需要这些！你有机会的时候再把 200 份纤维给我吧……不着急的！\"/pause 2000/end dialogue Emily \"No peeking! You'll see the end result soon.\"",
        "900553/t 600 1130/Hn ccPantry/A cc_Greenhouse/w sunny": "continue/64 15/farmer 64 16 2 Evelyn 64 18 0/skippable/pause 1500/speak Evelyn \"Good morning, dear. / 早上好，亲爱的。\"/pause 500/faceDirection Evelyn 3/pause 500/faceDirection Evelyn 2/speak Evelyn \"It was a lovely walk out here... I haven't seen this old farm in a long time.$s / 来这里散个步真好……我很久没有见过这个老农场了。$s#$b#It looks even better than I remember!$h / 它看起来比我记忆中的还要好！$h\"/pause 500/faceDirection Evelyn 3/faceDirection Evelyn 0/pause 500/speak Evelyn \"Here, I brought you a little something. / 给你，我给你带来了些小东西。#$b#It's a gift... from one gardener to another.$h / 一份礼物，一个园丁送给另一个园丁的礼物。$h\"/pause 800/itemAboveHead pot/playSound getNewSpecialItem/pause 3300/awardFestivalPrize pot/pause 200/message \"Received a 'Garden Pot' / 收到了一个“花盆”\"/pause 800/speak Evelyn \"These pots are really handy. You can use them to grow crops of any season indoors! / 这些花盆非常方便。你可以用它们在室内种植任何季节的作物！#$b#They also look nice outside... but out here they can only house in-season crops. / 放在室外，虽然看起来十分美观……但它们只能种当季的作物。\"/pause 500/speak Evelyn \"If you need more, they're really easy to make, too... here, I've got an old magazine clipping with instructions. / 如果你需要更多这样的花盆，也十分易于制作。我得到一本旧杂志的剪贴，上面有说明，请收下。\"/pause 200/playSound getNewSpecialItem/addCraftingRecipe Garden Pot/pause 500/message \"Learned how to craft a 'Garden Pot' / 学会如何制作“花盆”\"/pause 800/speak Evelyn \"Well, I'd better go. George gets grumpy if he doesn't have his oatmeal on time... / 好吧，我要走了。如果乔治没有按时吃燕麦片，他就会变得脾气暴躁。#$b#You have a great day, honey!$h / 甜心，祝你今天过得愉快！$h\"/pause 500/end",
        "65/m 25000/t 600 1200/H": "continue/64 15/farmer 64 16 2 Demetrius 64 18 0/pause 1500/speak Demetrius \"Hi @! I have some good news for you. A few days ago I made a breakthrough in my research on the local environment.$h / 嗨，@!我有好消息要告诉你。前几天，我对本地环境的研究取得了突破。$h#$b#I'll spare you the technical details and get to the point... You know that empty cave you have, over in the cliffs? / 技术细节我就不跟你说了，直接说结果……你知道往西一段距离的那个洞穴吧？#$b#Well, I have a way to turn it into something useful... for both of us. / 我有办法把它变成有用的东西了……对你我都有用。#$b#I'd like to set up the cave to attract some local species. That way I can observe them in a more controlled environment. And you can harvest whatever products they produce. / 我想利用那个洞吸引一些本地的物种。这样我就可以在一个更可控的环境下观察它们了。然后不管它们生出来啥都归你了。#$b#I can either set up the cave to attract mushrooms or fruit bats. The bats will sometimes leave fruit for you to collect. / 我也可以用这个洞吸引食菇蝠或果蝠。这些蝙蝠有时候会给你留下水果。\"/cave/speak Demetrius \"Alright! I'll go set it up for you right now! It shouldn't take any time at all.$h / 就这么说好了！我现在就给你收拾去！不会花很长时间的！$h#$b#Thanks for letting me do this. / 谢谢你给我这次机会。\"/end dialogue Demetrius \"I'm excited to see what happens with that cave. Aren't you?#$e#I hope you're pleased with the work I did.\"",
        "3912125/f Elliott 3500/O Elliott/t 500 1500/p Elliott/U 8": "continue/-10000 -1000/farmer -100 -100 2 Elliott -100 -100 2/addConversationTopic ElliottGone1 0/addConversationTopic elliottGone 6/addWorldState elliottGone/skippable/warp Elliott 63 15/warp farmer -100 -100/faceDirection Elliott 2/showFrame Elliott 38/viewport 64 15 clamp true/pause 1000/pause 2000/playSound doorClose/warp farmer 64 15/positionOffset farmer 0 16/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 3/emote farmer 8/pause 500/showFrame Elliott 39/emote Elliott 16/pause 500/speak Elliott \"@! I've just received the most exciting news! / @！我刚收到一个激动人心的消息！\"/pause 50/jump Elliott/pause 500/speak Elliott \"It's very short notice... but I've been invited to do a reading tour for my book, '%book'! / 通知很仓促……我受邀为我的书《%book》办一个巡回阅读会！\"/emote farmer 32/showFrame Elliott 0/faceDirection Elliott 1/pause 500/emote Elliott 28/pause 400/speak Elliott \"...I'll be out of town for a week. Will you be okay?$s / ……我要出城一个星期。你觉得可以吗？$s\"/quickQuestion #Yes, I'll be fine.#I'll be happy as a clam!#Don't go!(break)emote Elliott 20\\speak Elliott \"I'll miss you very much, my dear. / 我会一直想念你的，亲爱的。#$b#And I'll write to you every day, of course! / 当然，我每天都会给你写信！\"\\emote farmer 20(break)jump Elliott\\pause 500\\speak Elliott \"Hah... good one. Now, don't get too excited...$8#$b#I'll be sure to write to you every day. I'll miss you!\"(break)speak Elliott \"But, my dear... This is a rare opportunity for me. I must go!$s#$b#Please don't make me feel guilty about this. I'll write to you every day, and I'll be back before you know it.\"/pause 1000/animate Elliott true true 100 35/animate farmer true true 100 101/specificTemporarySprite heart 63 15/pause 2000/stopAnimation Elliott/showFrame Elliott 4/stopAnimation farmer/pause 500/speak Elliott \"I leave early tomorrow morning... / 我明天一早就走……#$b#I need to pack!$8 / 我现在要去整理行李！$8\"/end dialogue Elliott \"Don't let me forget my hairbrush, my hairspray, my fine-tooth comb, and my pomegranate conditioner!\"",
        "93/f Jodi 1000/t 600 930/d Tue Wed Thu Fri Sat Sun": "continue/64 15/farmer 64 16 2 Jodi 64 18 0/pause 1500/addQuest 22/skippable/speak Jodi \"*puff* ...hi @! *pant* Whew... that was quite a workout, walking all the way up here.$h / *呼*……嗨，@!*喘息* 呼咻……真是累死了……走上来真的好累。$h\"/pause 200/emote Jodi 28/pause 200/speak Jodi \"Anyway... I came by to ask if you wanted to have dinner with us tonight! / 话说……我是来邀请你与我们共进晚餐的！#$b#You don't have to... but if you decide to come, could you please bring a largemouth bass with you? / 你不用……不过如果你来的话，你能带条大嘴鲈鱼吗？#$b#...that's right. One of those big, slimy fish from the lake. I need one for the casserole I'm making.$h / ……没错。那种很大的，从湖里捞出来的黏糊糊的鱼。我要用一条大嘴鲈鱼炖砂锅。$h#$b#Okay, well... it'll be at our house at around 7:00 PM tonight... don't forget the largemouth bass! Bye. / 今晚七点在我们家……不要忘了带大嘴鲈鱼！再见。\"/pause 300/end dialogue Jodi \"Fish casserole always hits the spot.\"",
        "992253/t 600 1130/f Leah 1500/w sunny": "continue/64 15/farmer 64 16 2 Leah 64 18 0/pause 1500/speak Leah \"Hi, @. Beautiful day, isn't it? / 嗨，@。今天天气真好啊。\"/pause 500/speak Leah \"I brought you a gift. / 我给你带了件礼物。#$b#It's a sculpture I've been working on, just for you. / 这是我做的一个雕像，专门为你做的。\"/pause 500/pause 800/itemAboveHead sculpture/pause 3300/pause 800/awardFestivalPrize sculpture/pause 800/pause 50/speak Leah \"It's called... 'How I Feel About @'. I hope you like it. / 它叫……“我对@的感受”。希望你喜欢。\"/pause 50/pause 50/end",
        "63/y 2/t 600 1800/H": "continue/64 15/farmer 64 16 2 Kent 64 18 0/broadcastEvent/skippable/pause 1500/speak Kent \"Um, hello there. My name's Kent. I just got back last night... from overseas. My wife told me that a new farmer had moved in while I was gone. / 呃，你好啊，我的名字是肯特。我昨晚才回来……从海外回来。我老婆告诉我，在我不在的这段时间有个农夫搬过来了。\"/pause 500/speak Kent \"Well, I just wanted to introduce myself... I'll see you around. / 我只是来自我介绍一下……回头见。\"/pause 300/end",
        "47/f Sam 2000/t 600 800/e 44": "continue/64 15/farmer 64 16 2 Sam 64 18 0/pause 1500/speak Sam \"Hi @. Guess what? My band is playing a show tonight, in Zuzu City! / 嗨，@，你猜怎么着？我们乐队今晚要演出了，就在祖祖城！#$b#Meet me at the bus stop around 4:00 this afternoon to leave for the show. You better be there! / 今天下午4点在车站等我，然后一起去演出现场。你一定要来啊！\"/pause 300/end dialogue Sam \"I'm excited and a little nervous for the show tonight. I'm sure everything will turn out okay.\"",
        "992553/t 600 1130/n copperFound": "continue/64 15/farmer 64 16 2 Clint 64 18 0/skippable/pause 1500/speak Clint \"Uh... Hi there. Good morning. / 啊……嗨。早啊。#$b#I noticed that you've been breaking some rocks open and finding ore. That's good! / 我注意到你一直在凿石头找矿石。真的很棒！\"/pause 500/speak Clint \"If you want to get the most out of the ores you find, you'll need a furnace. / 如果你想尽可能多的找到矿石的话，你需要一个熔炉。\"/pause 500/speak Clint \"Just so happens I had an extra set of blueprints lying around. Here, I want you to have them. / 正巧我有个闲置的蓝图。给，你收下吧。\"/pause 800/itemAboveHead/playSound getNewSpecialItem/addCraftingRecipe Furnace/pause 3300/message \"Learned how to craft a 'Furnace' / 学会如何制造'熔炉'。\"/pause 800/speak Clint \"The furnace allows you to smelt metal bars. The bars can be used for crafting, construction, and tool upgrades. / 你可以用熔炉来融化金属棒。这些金属棒可以用来锻造，建造，以及升级工具。\"/pause 500/faceDirection Clint 1/pause 500/faceDirection Clint 0/speak Clint \" When you've smelted a few copper bars, consider having me upgrade one of your tools. It can make your work a lot easier. / 当你融化一定数量的铜棒时，可以考虑让我给你升级一件工具。你的工作会变得更加轻松。#$b#Well, okay. I'm heading home. Take it easy. / 那好。我回去了。慢慢来。\"/pause 200/addQuest 11/end",
        "55/f Leah 2000/t 600 800/z winter/n LeahArtShowSuggestion": "continue/64 15/farmer 64 16 2 Leah 64 18 0/pause 1500/speak Leah \"Hi @! Are you free this afternoon? / 嗨，@！今天下午有空吗？#$b#I finally got my act together and I'm doing my art show tonight in the town square!$h / 我终于走出泥潭了，今晚我就要在广场表演我的艺术！$h#$b#Come into town between 3:00 and 5:00 pm if you want to be there! / 如果你想来的话，就下午 3:00 到 5:00 之间来镇里！\"/pause 300/end dialogue Leah \"I'm nervous...$l\"",
        "2118991/e 3910975/t 600 800": "continue/64 15/farmer 64 16 2 Shane 64 18 0/pause 1500/skippable/speak Shane \"Hey... / 嘿……\"/pause 500/faceDirection Shane 1/pause 500/faceDirection Shane 0/speak Shane \"Oh man... Uh... How do I say this?$s / 噢，伙计……嗯……怎么说？$s#$b#I'm really sorry about what happened at the cliffs. That was... embarrassing... / 关于在悬崖上发生的事情，我很抱歉。真是……令人尴尬……\"/pause 500/speak Shane \"$q -1 null#   /   #$r -1 10 event_apologize1#I'm glad I was there to help. / 我很高兴我能帮到忙。#$r -1 -10 event_apologize2#You needed a serious wake-up call. / 你需要一个正式的警钟。#$r -1 10 event_apologize3#I'm just happy you're still here. / 我很高兴你还活着。\"/pause 1000/faceDirection Shane 1/pause 1000/speak Shane \"I've decided I want to see a therapist. Harvey got me in touch with a colleague of his...$s / 我要去看心理医生。哈维让我与他的同事联系……$s\"/pause 500/faceDirection Shane 0/speak Shane \"Anyway... I just wanted to thank you for taking care of me. And I want you to know that I'm going to take things a little more seriously from now on. / 无论如何……我只是想谢谢你照顾我。我想让你知道，我要从现在开始认真对待事情。#$b#I don't want to be a burden on anyone... / 我不想成为任何人的负担……\"/pause 1000/faceDirection Shane 1 true/pause 50/faceDirection Shane 2/pause 500/showFrame Shane 19/pause 2000/end"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Events/FarmHouse",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "3918601/e 3918600/O Sam/t 610 1700/A samJob1/p Sam/L": "distantBanjo/-1000 -1000/farmer 52 24 1 Sam 53 24 0/addConversationTopic samJob2 2/skippable/makeInvisible 52 24/animate Sam false true 400 43 51/viewport -100 -100 true unfreeze/pause 4000/stopAnimation Sam/showFrame Sam 39/pause 400/jump Sam/emote Sam 16/pause 500/speak Sam \"Hey @, listen to this!$8 / 嘿，听听这个！$8\"/pause 500/stopAnimation Sam/animate Sam false true 400 43 51/pause 500/speak Sam \"'Dear Sam, we are pleased to offer you a position as 'junior composer' at Zuzu Broadcasting Group, TV division...'$6 / “亲爱的山姆，我们很高兴为您提供一个祖祖广播集团电视部的初级作曲家职位……”$6#$b#Wow! Music for a TV show! How cool is that?!$h / 哇哦！为一个电视节目做音乐！这也太酷了吧？！$h\"/pause 500/emote Sam 40/pause 1000/textAboveHead Sam \"Oh... / 哦……\"/animate Sam false true 400 43 51/pause 1000/speak Sam \"Oh... Hold on...$s / 哦……等等……$s#$b#... It's a TV show for little kids... 'The Happy Junimo Show'$s / ……这是一个给小孩子看的电视节目……“欢乐祝尼魔表演”$s\"/emote Sam 28/pause 1000/speak Sam \"Not exactly what I had in mind...$s / 跟我想的不太一样……$s\"/stopAnimation Sam/showFrame Sam 0/pause 300/faceDirection Sam 3/pause 1000/quickQuestion #Just think of this as a stepping stone in your career...#Just think of how happy you'll make the children!#I'm sorry...(break)pause 100\\speak Sam \"Hmm... Yeah, I guess that's one way to look at it.$7 / 嗯……是啊，这也是一种看待这份工作的方式。$7\"(break)pause 100\\speak Sam \"I mean... you're right, someone's gotta make children's music. But it's not exactly a 'dream job'...$7\"(break)pause 100\\speak Sam \"Ah well... that's okay. I'll make the best of it, like I always do.$7\"/pause 1000/faceDirection Sam 0/speak Sam \"I guess I'd better start 'thinking like a kid'... / 我想我最好得开始“用小孩的思考方式”了……\"/quickQuestion #That should be easy for you...#You could ask your little brother for help!(break)animate Sam false true 100 33\\shake Sam 4000\\pause 500\\textAboveHead Sam \"Hey! / 嘿！\"\\faceDirection farmer 2 true\\animate farmer false true 200 102 103(break)pause 100\\speak Sam \"Hmm... That's not a bad idea. At the very least, I could play him my songs and see if he likes them.#$b#Thanks for the advice, @.$10\"/pause 2000/end dialogue Sam \"I'll be working on this for a few days.\"",
        "558291/y 3/H": "grandpas_theme/-2000 -1000/farmer 13 23 2/broadcastEvent/addTemporaryActor Grandpa 1 1 -100 -100 2 true/specificTemporarySprite grandpaSpirit/viewport -1000 -1000 true/pause 10000/speak Grandpa \"My dear boy... / 我亲爱的孩子……^My dearest grand-daughter... / 我亲爱的孙女……#$b#It's been many years since we last spoke. You were just a little boy... Do you remember? / 自从我们最后一次讲话，已经过去了很多年。你那时还很小……记得吗？^It's been many years since we last spoke. You were just a little girl... Do you remember? / 自从我们最后一次讲话，已经过去了很多年。你那时还是个小姑娘……记得吗？#$b#Look how far you've come! / 你现在已经长大了啊！#$b#Though you may have forgotten me, I've been here all along. / 虽然你也许已经忘了我，但我一直都陪着你。#$b#You see... My body has departed this world, but my heart will always remain in Stardew Valley. / 虽然……我的身体离开了这个世界，但我的心永远留在星露谷。\"/specificTemporarySprite grandpaNight/pause 4000/speak Grandpa \"You've been here two years now... / 你来到这里已经两年了……\"/grandpaEvaluation/pause 3000/speak Grandpa \"The future of %farm Farm is in your hands, now. / %farm的未来掌握在你手里。#$b#Farewell! / 再见！\"/pause 1000/globalFade/removeTemporarySprites/playMusic none/pause 1000/end bed",
        "3917626/f Harvey 3500/O Harvey/t 2000 2400/p Harvey/L": "harveys_theme_jazz/-1000 -1000/farmer -100 -100 0 Harvey 22 24 0/skippable/ambientLight 0 0 0/makeInvisible 19 24 6 1/specificTemporarySprite harveyKitchenSetup/viewport 22 24 true/pause 3000/showFrame Harvey 19/playSound clank/shake Harvey 200/pause 450/playSound clank/shake Harvey 200/pause 450/playSound clank/shake Harvey 200/pause 750/showFrame Harvey 53/pause 100/playSound sipTea/pause 1000/textAboveHead Harvey \"Needs salt... / 需要加盐……\"/stopAnimation Harvey/pause 800/move Harvey -1 0 0/pause 2000/showFrame Harvey 19/playSound bubbles/pause 1000/playSound bubbles/pause 2000/stopAnimation Harvey/move Harvey 1 0 0/pause 2000/playSound furnace/specificTemporarySprite harveyKitchenFlame/pause 500/jump Harvey/pause 500/textAboveHead Harvey \"It's burning! / 烧起来了！\"/pause 500/speed Harvey 8/move Harvey -2 0 0/pause 100/speed Harvey 8/move Harvey 2 0 0/pause 100/speed Harvey 8/move Harvey -2 0 0/pause 100/speed Harvey 8/move Harvey 2 0 0/pause 3000/move Harvey 2 0 0/pause 500/showFrame Harvey 19/playSound openChest/pause 1000/textAboveHead Harvey \"Hmm... / 嗯……\"/pause 3000/stopAnimation Harvey/move Harvey -2 0 0/pause 500/showFrame Harvey 19/textAboveHead Harvey \"A little bit of this... / 加点这个……\"/playSound dropItemInWater/pause 2000/stopAnimation Harvey/move Harvey -3 0 0/pause 1000/showFrame Harvey 19/playSound coin/pause 500/stopAnimation Harvey/move Harvey 3 0 0/pause 250/showFrame Harvey 19/pause 500/textAboveHead Harvey \"Some of this... / 一些这个……\"/pause 600/playSound slosh/pause 2000/showFrame Harvey 53/pause 200/playSound sipTea/pause 2000/showFrame Harvey 4/jump Harvey/textAboveHead Harvey \"Presto! / 快！\"/pause 2000/warp farmer 27 30/playSound doorClose/move farmer 0 -1 0/pause 500/stopAnimation Harvey/faceDirection Harvey 2/speak Harvey \"Ah... You're right on time, @!$h / 啊……你回来的正是时候，@！$h#$b#Let me just set the table... / 让我摆一下盘……\"/pause 300/fade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 2000/playMusic none/pause 3000/makeInvisible 20 24 4 2/ambientLight 180 180 0/playMusic kindadumbautumn/showFrame Harvey 51/positionOffset Harvey -8 0/faceDirection farmer 1/showFrame 117/specificTemporarySprite harveyDinnerSet/pause 4000/speak Harvey \"You've been working so hard on the farm... I wanted to make you a special dinner. / 你在农场工作得这么辛苦，我想给你做一顿特别的晚餐。\"/emote farmer 20/speak Harvey \"It's my very own 'angel hair pasta primavera'... with clams!$h / 这是我自制的“天使之发·春之意面”……里面有蛤贝！$h\"/animate Harvey false true 300 51 52/pause 300/playSound eat/pause 600/playSound eat/pause 600/playSound eat/pause 500/animate Harvey false true 100 51/quickQuestion #It tastes heavenly#It tastes healthy#It tastes watery#It tastes burnt#It tastes like your moustache#It tastes like fungus(break)speak Harvey \"Heavenly, huh? That must be the 'angel hair'!$h / 要上天了，是吧？那肯定是“天使之发”！$h#$b#I'm glad you like it! You deserve the best.$l / 我很高兴你喜欢它！你应该得到最好的。$l\"(break)speak Harvey \"Oh yes, I forgot to mention... it's 'whole wheat' pasta. And it's brimming with fresh vegetables.#$b#It's important that you eat healthy food! I want you to live forever...$l\"(break)speak Harvey \"Oh... I see. I knew I needed to add more salt.$s#$b#Well, at least you'll be well hydrated.$s\"(break)emote Harvey 28\\speak Harvey \"Oh... I thought I gave myself the burnt one.$s#$b#Um, I lost track of one the pans and it caught fire... Sorry, dear.$s\"(break)jump Harvey\\pause 500\\speak Harvey \"Uhhh...! Heh. I guess a piece of my moustache may have fallen into the pasta...$8#$b#Well! Extra fiber, right? Heh... (sorry honey)$8\"(break)jump Harvey\\pause 400\\speak Harvey \"Oh! Eh... Must've been the truffle oil I drizzled on top...$8#$b#You meant delicious, edible fungus... right honey? Of course... Heh.$8\"/pause 2000/animate Harvey false true 300 51 52/speak Harvey \"So, tell me about your day... / 那么，跟我说说你今天都做了什么……\"/quickQuestion #I tended the farm#I dug around in the caves#I spent the day fishing#I socialized in town#I did a little of everything#I can't remember#I didn't do anything(break)speak Harvey \"Yes, I can still see the dirt in your hair! I really appreciate all the hard work you do, honey. / 真好，我仍然可以看到你头发上的污垢！亲爱的，我真的很感谢你的辛勤工作。\"(break)speak Harvey \"That sounds dangerous... are you sure that's safe?$8#$b#I don't want to see you on the operating table anytime soon...$s#$b#Although I have to say, I like how courageous you are...$l\"(break)speak Harvey \"A peaceful day by the water, huh? That sounds very relaxing.#$b#I'm glad you're having fun out there!$h\"(break)speak Harvey \"Ah, that's good. Having an active social life is healthy for the brain.#$b#But remember, I'm always here for you if you need someone to talk to!$l\"(break)speak Harvey \"That makes sense. There's lots to do in this valley! ...And I know how hard you work.#$b#Just remember to take breaks! When you're so busy, it's easy to get burnt out from exhaustion.\"(break)speak Harvey \"Ah... I have that problem, too. The boundary between days can blur together... it's hard to keep track of everything!\"(break)speak Harvey \"Took the day off, huh? I'm glad to hear it.#$b#Well, with a day off and a hearty dinner you'll be fully re-charged for tomorrow.\"/pause 1000/stopAnimation Harvey/showFrame Harvey 51/speak Harvey \"Whew... I'm stuffed! That was great... / 哇，我吃的很饱！这可真棒……\"/emote farmer 20/pause 1000/playMusic nightTime/speak Harvey \"I'll take care of the dishes... / 我来洗碗……\"/pause 400/emote farmer 60/pause 250/speak Harvey \"Don't feel bad... I like to do nice things for you! It makes me happy. / 别感觉不安……我喜欢为你做事情！这使我很快乐。\"/pause 1000/speak Harvey \"I know I say this a lot, but... marrying you was the best thing that ever happened to me!$l / 我知道我说过很多次了，但是……和你结婚是我遇到的最好的事情！$l\"/emote farmer 20/pause 1000/fade/viewport -100 -100/end dialogue Harvey \"That was filling. I'm gonna sleep well...\"",
        "3917601/f Emily 3500/O Emily/n emilyFiber/A emilyFiber/t 2000 2400/p Emily": "EmilyTheme/-1000 -1000/farmer 8 14 3 Emily 7 14 1/makeInvisible 8 14/viewport -100 -100 true unfreeze/pause 3000/speak Emily \"Welcome home, @. I hope you had a nice day. / 欢迎回家，@。希望你今天过得愉快。\"/pause 1000/emote farmer 20/pause 1200/speak Emily \"So... I finished that secret project I was working on. / 嗯……我已经把正在进行的秘密工程做完了。\"/emote farmer 8/pause 500/speak Emily \"It's a brand new hand-made outfit for you!$h / 这是一套全新的，为你做的手造工具！$h\"/pause 500/awardFestivalPrize emilyClothes/pause 500/playSound coin/message \"Received Emily's Magic Hat, Emily's Magic Boots, Emily's Magic Shirt, and a matching set of pants! / 收到了艾米丽的魔法帽、艾米丽的魔法靴、艾米丽的魔法上衣和配套的裤子！\"/pause 500/speak Emily \"I've always loved sewing and making crafts... So I thought it'd be nice to make you something by hand. I had a lot of fun! / 我一直喜欢缝纫和制作工艺品……所以我觉得为你做些手制品很不错。我做的很开心！#$b#I hope it fits right... and that the fiber isn't too itchy. / 我希望你穿起来合身……而且这些纤维制品不会让你身体发痒。#$b#There's boots, a hat, a shirt, and pants! It's a complete outfit. / 我做了靴子、帽子、上衣和裤子！是一套完整的衣装。\"/pause 800/speak Emily \"Now, when you wear those clothes, you'll think of me... and you'll know I'm here waiting for you to come home safe... okay?$l / 现在，当你穿上这些衣服时，你会想起我……你会知道我在这里等你平安回家……好吗？$l\"/pause 500/faceDirection Emily 2/pause 500/animate Emily false true 250 52 53/pause 250/playSound dwop/positionOffset Emily 4 0/pause 250/pause 250/playSound dwop/positionOffset Emily 4 0/pause 250/pause 250/playSound dwop/positionOffset Emily 4 0/pause 250/pause 250/playSound dwop/positionOffset Emily 4 0/pause 250/pause 250/playSound dwop/positionOffset Emily 4 0/pause 250/pause 250/playSound dwop/faceDirection farmer 2 true/positionOffset Emily 4 0/pause 250/pause 250/playSound dwop/positionOffset Emily 4 0/pause 250/pause 250/playSound dwop/positionOffset Emily 4 0/pause 250/stopAnimation Emily/pause 3000/showFrame Emily 55/pause 500/eyes 1 -4500/pause 3000/fade/viewport -100 -100/pause 500/end dialogue Emily \"Time for bed.\"",
        "558292/e 321777/t 600 620/H": "grandpas_theme/-2000 -1000/farmer 13 23 2/broadcastEvent/addTemporaryActor Grandpa 1 1 -100 -100 2 true/skippable/specificTemporarySprite grandpaSpirit/viewport -1000 -1000 true/pause 10000/speak Grandpa \"My dear boy... / 我亲爱的孩子……^My dearest grand-daughter... / 我亲爱的孙女……#$b#I'm glad you summoned me. I... was perhaps a little too harsh with you last time. / 我很高兴你召唤了我。也许上次我对你太严厉了。#$b#Forgive me. You've been working very hard, and I'm proud of it. / 请原谅我。你一直那么努力，我真为你感到骄傲。\"/specificTemporarySprite grandpaNight/pause 4000/speak Grandpa \"Let's see... / 那么……\"/grandpaEvaluation2/pause 3000/globalFade/removeTemporarySprites/playMusic none/pause 1000/end bed",
        "3918602/e 3918601/O Sam/t 610 1700/A samJob2/p Sam/L": "none/-1000 -1000/farmer 52 24 1 Sam 53 24 3/addConversationTopic samJob3 3/skippable/makeInvisible 52 24/viewport -100 -100 true unfreeze/pause 2000/speak Sam \"Hey, @. I'm making progress on the song... check it out. / 嘿，这首歌我写的差不多了，来听听看。\"/pause 400/faceDirection Sam 2/animate Sam false true 400 52 53/playMusic sam_acoustic2/pause 26000/stopAnimation Sam/showFrame Sam 52/pause 1000/showFrame Sam 0/faceDirection Sam 3/speak Sam \"It's kinda bare-bones right now... but when I add in all the different instruments, it'll come together. You'll see. / 目前听起来还有点单薄……但是，如果我把各种乐器都加进去的时候，它们会融为一体。你会理解的。\"/emote farmer 32/speak Sam \"You know... I'm not too upset about this kid's show idea anymore. / 那个……我对这个儿童节目的主意已经不再忐忑不安了。#$b#You gotta start somewhere, right? / 一切总有个开始，是吧？#$b#And hey, maybe I'll be a big hit in the children's concert circuit!$h / 而且呢，也许我会在儿童音乐会上大受欢迎！$h\"/emote farmer 56/pause 1200/end dialogue Sam \"I'll have the finished song ready soon. I hope they're happy with it!\"",
        "8675611/e 6184643/O Haley/A haleyCakewalk1/t 620 1700/p Haley": "continue/-1000 -1000/farmer 23 24 3 Haley 22 24 1/makeInvisible 23 24/addQuest 127/addConversationTopic haleyCakewalk2 0/skippable/viewport -100 -100 true unfreeze/pause 3000/speak Haley \"Hi, honey. / 嗨，亲爱的。#$b#Hey... I have an idea... I want to get everyone together for a charity cake-walk. / 嘿……我有个主意……我想让大家聚在一起做慈善蛋糕竞走赛。\"/pause 500/emote farmer 8/pause 1000/speak Haley \"Uh... It's kind of like musical chairs, but everyone wins and gets cake! You'll see...$h / 啊……这有点像抢座位游戏，但每个人都会赢，会得到蛋糕！你会见识到的……$h#$b#It'll be on the next sunny day in the town square. / 之后找一个阳光明媚的日子，在镇里广场上开展怎么样？#$b#Um... would you mind bringing a chocolate cake? / 嗯……你可以带个巧克力蛋糕来吗？\"/quickQuestion Do you agree to bring chocolate cake?#Yes#Yes (begrudgingly)(break)speak Haley \"Great! I'll meet you in the town square tomorrow, weather permitting.$h / 太好了！如果天气好的话，我明天会在镇上的广场和你见面。$h\"\\animate Haley false true 100 28\\animate farmer true true 100 101\\positionOffset Haley 8 0\\positionOffset farmer -8 0(break)emote Haley 12\\speak Haley \"What's up with the snarky attitude?$3#$b#Fine. You're going to show up tomorrow with a chocolate cake, or else you're in the dog house. You like that better?$3\"/pause 2000/fade/viewport -1000 -1000/end dialogue Haley \"I'm bringing a pink cake.\"",
        "4325434/f Penny 3500/O Penny/t 1500 1900/p Penny": "sweet/-1000 -1000/farmer 26 24 3 Penny 23 24 0/animate Penny false true 250 24 25/makeInvisible 20 15 5 1/makeInvisible 23 24 5 1/viewport -100 -100 true unfreeze/move farmer -2 0 3/pause 1000/stopAnimation Penny/pause 20/playSound thudStep/pause 250/faceDirection Penny 1/pause 50/animate Penny true true 100 20/pause 1000/stopAnimation Penny/faceDirection Penny 1/pause 200/speak Penny \"Welcome home, honey... How was your day? / 欢迎回家，亲爱的……今天过得怎么样？\"/quickQuestion #It was fine#Not good...#It was fantastic!(break)speak Penny \"Just business as usual, huh? / 就跟往常一样，是吗？#$b#Well, I've got a zesty new recipe in the oven, so maybe things will get a little more exciting!$h / 唔，我的烤箱里有一个很有意思的新菜，所以也许今天会变得有些令人激动！$h\"(break)emote Penny 28\\speak Penny \"Oh, I'm sorry!$s#$b#Well, you're back now... I'll do my best to make you feel better.\"(break)speak Penny \"That's great! I'm glad you enjoy your work so much.$h\"/speak Penny \"I'm happy you're home.$l / 我很高兴你回家了。$l\"/pause 500/animate Penny false true 100 35/animate farmer true true 100 101/positionOffset farmer -8 0/positionOffset Penny 8 0/pause 1500/positionOffset Penny -8 0/stopAnimation Penny/showFrame Penny 4/stopAnimation farmer/pause 1000/speak Penny \"Oh, you smell like the outdoors...$l / 哦，你有一股户外的气息……$l#$b#It's nice...$11 / 这很不错……$11\"/pause 1000/animate Penny false true 150 4 5 6 7/positionOffset Penny 2 0/pause 100/positionOffset Penny 2 0/pause 100/positionOffset Penny 2 0/pause 100/positionOffset Penny 2 0/pause 100/positionOffset Penny 2 0/pause 100/positionOffset Penny 2 0/pause 100/positionOffset Penny 2 0/pause 100/positionOffset Penny 2 0/pause 100/positionOffset Penny 2 0/pause 100/positionOffset Penny 2 0/stopAnimation Penny/showFrame Penny 21/pause 800/speak Penny \"You know... I really appreciate the hard work you do for the family. / 是这样……我真的很感激你为家庭所做的努力。#$b#So it's important to me that when you come home, the house is nice and cozy, and everything's in order! / 所以对我来说，重要的是当你回家的时候，房子整洁舒适，一切都井井有条！\"/emote farmer 20/speak Penny \"So I was thinking... I'd like to re-decorate the bedroom with some of my own hand-made decor! / 所以……我想用我自己的一些手工装饰重新装饰卧室！#$b#But first, I have to ask you...$11 / 但首先，我得问问你……$11\"/quickQuestion What style do you prefer?#Forest And Moon: Peaceful Blue#Strawberry Home#Pirate Theme#I don't want any changes!(break)addConversationTopic pennyRedecorating 2\\addMailReceived pennyQuilt0\\speak Penny \"Ah... something soothing. Okay! / 啊……要能够抚慰人心的装饰。交给我吧！#$b#Just give me a few days, then. / 给我几天时间。#$b#I won't touch any of your chests, but it would be nice if you could move them out of the bedroom. / 我不会碰你的箱子，但如果你能把它们搬出卧室就好了。\"(break)addConversationTopic pennyRedecorating 2\\addMailReceived pennyQuilt1\\speak Penny \"Something warm and inviting, huh? That works for me!#$b#Just give me a few days, then.#$b#I won't touch any of your chests, but it would be nice if you could move them out of the bedroom.\"(break)addConversationTopic pennyRedecorating 2\\addMailReceived pennyQuilt2\\speak Penny \"Heh... Okay. Whatever you like, honey.$h#$b#Just give me a few days, then.#$b#I won't touch any of your chests, but it would be nice if you could move them out of the bedroom.\"(break)addMailReceived noQuilt\\speak Penny \"Oh! Okay... I won't worry about it, then.$s\"/pause 500/showFrame Penny 4/playSound crystal/jump Penny/pause 500/speak Penny \"Oh! The pop-overs are ready. / 哦！蟹黄糕准备好了。\"/faceDirection Penny 3/animate Penny false true 150 12 13 14 15/positionOffset Penny -4 0/pause 50/positionOffset Penny -4 0/pause 50/positionOffset Penny -4 0/pause 50/positionOffset Penny -4 0/pause 50/stopAnimation Penny/move Penny -1 0 0/faceDirection Penny 0/pause 100/showFrame Penny 29/pause 150/showFrame Penny 30/playSound openChest/pause 1300/showFrame Penny 28/playSound coin/emote farmer 20/move farmer -1 0 3/farmerEat 203/showFrame Penny 4/pause 2000/playSound gulp/emote Penny 32/pause 1000/faceDirection farmer 3/end dialogue Penny \"Make yourself comfortable, dear.\"",
        "4324303/e 4325434/O Penny/A pennyRedecorating/l noQuilt/B": "spring_day_ambient/-1000 -1000/farmer 27 13 0 Penny 26 13 1/fade unfade/makeInvisible 26 13/makeInvisible 20 4/eyes 1 -10/positionOffset farmer 0 8/viewport -100 -100 true unfreeze/pause 1000/emote farmer 24/pause 3000/showFrame Penny 21/startJittering/pause 500/stopJittering/showFrame Penny 4/pause 500/speak Penny \"@... Good morning...$11 / @……早上好……$11\"/pause 1000/showFrame Penny 21/startJittering/pause 500/stopJittering/showFrame Penny 4/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 3/emote Penny 32/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 2/emote farmer 16/jump farmer/pause 1000/animate Penny false true 150 4 5 6 7/positionOffset Penny 2 0/pause 100/positionOffset Penny 2 0/pause 100/positionOffset Penny 2 0/pause 100/positionOffset Penny 2 0/pause 100/positionOffset Penny 2 0/pause 100/positionOffset Penny 2 0/pause 100/positionOffset Penny 2 0/pause 100/positionOffset Penny 2 0/pause 100/positionOffset Penny 2 0/pause 100/positionOffset Penny 2 0/stopAnimation Penny/showFrame Penny 21/pause 500/speak Penny \"Notice anything unusually soft? I quilted this custom bedspread by hand.$11 / 注意到有什么变得柔软了吗？这个床罩是我亲手做的。$11\"/eyes -1 2000/startJittering/pause 2000/stopJittering/speak Penny \"So, what do you think?$11 / 所以，你觉得怎么样？$11\"/quickQuestion #Looks great!#I don't like it.(break)emote Penny 20\\speak Penny \"I'm glad you like it. The house is starting to look really cozy, isn't it?$h / 我很高兴你喜欢它。房子开始变得越来越很舒适了，不是吗？$h\"\\faceDirection Penny 2\\faceDirection farmer 2\\emote farmer 20\\faceDirection farmer 3\\faceDirection Penny 1\\pause 1000\\animate Penny false true 100 35\\animate farmer true true 100 101(break)emote Penny 28\\speak Penny \"Oh.. okay.$s#$b#I put the old furniture in a chest... feel free to change it back...$s\"\\faceDirection Penny 3/pause 3000/fade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 500/message \"Penny's been working very hard around the house... / 佩妮一直在家里辛勤工作……\"/pause 500/message \"It really feels like home! / 这真的很有家的感觉！\"/pause 2000/end",
        "3918600/f Sam 3500/O Sam/t 610 1700/p Sam/L": "distantBanjo/-1000 -1000/farmer 50 24 1 Sam 53 24 0/addConversationTopic samJob1 2/skippable/makeInvisible 52 24/makeInvisible 51 24/makeInvisible 50 24/viewport -100 -100 true unfreeze/pause 3000/emote Sam 28/pause 500/move farmer 2 0 1/emote farmer 8/faceDirection Sam 3/pause 400/speak Sam \"Oh, hey @. You look like you've been working hard out there! / 哦，嘿，@。看起来你在努力工作！\"/pause 100/faceDirection Sam 0/emote Sam 40/pause 500/speak Sam \"Hey, I was just thinking...$s / 嘿，我是在想……$s#$b#You know, I really like living here with you. I mean... I love it! / 那个，我真的很喜欢和你住在一起。我的意思是……我很爱这样的生活！#$b#But, I feel like I've gotten really lazy. I just bum around aimlessly every day.$s / 不过，我觉得自己变得太游手好闲了。我每天漫无目的地闲逛。$s\"/pause 500/emote farmer 20/faceDirection Sam 3/speak Sam \"Oh, I know you don't mind! You make enough money on the farm that I don't really need to work, and I really appreciate that! / 哦，我知道你不介意！因为你在农场赚了足够的钱，所以我不需要去努力工作，对此我真的很感激！#$b#But I want to feel like I'm contributing to something... know what I mean? / 但我想让自己能为一些事情做出贡献……你懂我的意思吗？\"/faceDirection Sam 0/pause 400/speak Sam \"So... I think I'm gonna try to find some work... something to do with music. / 所以……我想我会努力去找一些工作……与音乐有关。#$b#That's always been what I love the most!$h / 毕竟这是我最爱的东西！$h#$b#Oh, uh... besides you, of course!$8 / 哦，呃……当然，我也最爱你！$8#$b#Heh...$10 / 嘿……$10\"/faceDirection Sam 3/speak Sam \"Anyway... I'll let you know how it goes! / 不管怎样……我会把我最近的成果告诉你的！\"/emote farmer 32/pause 500/end",
        "3917666/f Maru 3500/O Maru/t 610 1700/p Maru/d Sun/z winter": "sweet/-1000 -1000/farmer 23 24 3 Maru 22 24 1/makeInvisible 23 24/viewport -100 -100 true unfreeze/pause 3000/speak Maru \"Hi Honey. / 嗨，亲爱的。#$b#Tomorrow night, there's a rare astronomical event happening... A comet is passing very close to our planet! / 明晚，会有一个罕见的天文现象……一颗彗星会从离我们星球很近的地方经过！#$b#I was thinking... maybe we should observe it together?$l / 我在想……或许我们可以一起去看？$l\"/pause 100/emote farmer 32/speak Maru \"Great!$h / 太好了！$h#$b#Meet me in the mountains at midnight tomorrow night. / 明晚午夜到山里跟我碰头。#$b#If it rains, we'll do it on the next night... the comet is here for a few days. / 如果晚上下雨，我们就第二天晚上再去看……这几天能看见彗星。\"/pause 500/pause 500/end",
        "3912132/e 3912126/O Elliott/A elliottGone/B": "spring_day_ambient/-1000 -1000/farmer 27 13 2 Elliott 25 13 1/fade unfade/makeInvisible 25 13/makeInvisible 26 13/makeInvisible 20 4/makeInvisible 22 4/eyes 1 -6000/viewport -100 -100 true unfreeze/pause 3000/emote farmer 24/pause 2000/speak Elliott \"@... I'm back... / @……我回来了……\"/jump farmer/pause 1000/move farmer -1 0 3/animate Elliott true true 100 35/animate farmer true true 100 101/positionOffset farmer -16 0/specificTemporarySprite heart 63 15/pause 2000/stopAnimation Elliott/showFrame Elliott 4/stopAnimation farmer/pause 1000/speak Elliott \"Ah... I've missed you.$l / 啊……我好想你。$l#$b#One drop of the big city and I'm quenched... I much prefer being back here with you! / 大城市让我喘不过气来……我更喜欢回到小镇上和你待在一起！\"/emote farmer 20/pause 300/speak Elliott \"Well, I guess it's back to the old routine once again!$h / 嗯，我觉得是时候回到日常生活啦！$h#$b#I've got some chores to catch up on... / 落下的家务事还没做呢……\"/pause 1000/end dialogue Elliott \"It's good to be back...\"",
        "3918603/e 3918602/O Sam/t 610 1700/A samJob3/p Sam/L": "distantBanjo/-1000 -1000/farmer 51 27 0 Sam 51 24 2 Jas 53 27 0 Vincent 52 27 0/skippable/makeInvisible 52 27/makeInvisible 53 27/makeInvisible 51 27/specificTemporarySprite samTV/viewport -100 -100 true unfreeze/pause 2000/speak Vincent \"I'm really excited, Sam! / 我真的很激动，山姆！\"/jump Vincent/pause 1000/speak Sam \"Okay, okay, Vince... I'm gonna put the song on right away.$h / 好吧，好吧，文森特……我马上就听这首歌。$h#$b#Now, you gotta listen really close, so you can tell me if you like it afterwards. Okay? / 好了，你要帮我仔细听听，然后告诉我你是不是喜欢。行吗？\"/pause 500/jump Vincent/textAboveHead Vincent \"OK! / 好的！\"/pause 1500/playMusic none/faceDirection Sam 1/pause 3000/playSound openBox/pause 2000/playMusic sam_acoustic1/pause 1000/specificTemporarySprite junimoShow/pause 2000/faceDirection Sam 2 true/pause 9000/animate Vincent false true 100 8 21 8 20/pause 11000/animate Jas false true 100 8 9 10 11/pause 23000/stopAnimation Jas/stopAnimation Vincent/jump Vincent/pause 800/jump Jas/pause 500/jump Vincent/pause 800/jump Jas/pause 500/jump Vincent/pause 800/jump Jas/pause 500/speak Jas \"I loved it!$h / 我超喜欢！$h\"/textAboveHead Vincent \"Me too! / 我也是！\"/pause 1500/jump Sam/pause 1000/emote Sam 20/pause 500/speak Sam \"Wow! I wasn't expecting such an overwhelming response!$8 / 真的吗！我没想到反响这么热烈！$8#$b#That's great! This is really fun!$h / 太好了！真的太有意思了！$h\"/pause 50/faceDirection Vincent 1 true/faceDirection Jas 3 true/move Sam 0 2 2/move Sam -1 0 2/move Sam 0 1 1/faceDirection farmer 3/speak Sam \"Hey, thanks for all the support with this. / 嘿，谢谢你对我的支持。#$b#You know... I kind of like making children's music. It's not very glamorous, but I'm making these kids really happy. That's important!$h / 是这样的……我有点喜欢上制作儿童音乐了。虽然这不是很令人向往的事情，但我让这些孩子真正收获了快乐。这才是重要的！$h\"/pause 100/emote farmer 20/pause 500/speak Sam \"Here, I wanted to give you this. It's a boombox with the song on it... So you can listen to it whenever you want. / 给，我想把这个交给你。这个音响里面有我的歌……这样你就可以想听就听了。\"/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 2/itemAboveHead samBoombox/pause 4200/awardFestivalPrize samBoombox/pause 1500/end dialogue Sam \"I'm just glad to know that my music makes people happy...\"",
        "9333220/e 9333219/O Sebastian/A sebastianFrog/t 620 1900": "distantBanjo/-1000 -1000/farmer 51 25 2 Sebastian 52 25 2/addWorldState sebastianFrog/addConversationTopic sebastianFrog2 6/specificTemporarySprite sebastianFrogHouse/skippable/makeInvisible 44 16 4 4/makeInvisible 50 25 4 4/viewport -100 -100 true unfreeze/pause 3000/faceDirection farmer 1/emote farmer 8/speak Sebastian \"Our little friend's doing much better, see? / 看到了吗？我们的小朋友做的好多了。\"/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 250/showFrame farmer 4/pause 800/showFrame Sebastian 51/playSound thudStep/pause 800/speak Sebastian \"...but I don't think he can go back into the wild... he's not fast enough to avoid predators anymore. / ……但我觉得没法把他放生……他跑得不够快，没法躲避捕食者。#$b#...So I set up this terrarium. / ……所以我做了这个生物育养箱。#$b#He looks happy, doesn't he?$h / 他看起来很高兴，不是吗？$h\"/pause 400/emote farmer 32/pause 500/showFrame farmer 0/pause 400/faceDirection farmer 1/speak Sebastian \"I wonder if he'll get lonely, though... / 不过，我觉得他可能会感到孤独……\"/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 600/quickQuestion #Why not start a 'frog sanctuary'?#He'll be fine.(break)speak Sebastian \"...a haven for frogs and toads who can't make it on their own? Not a bad idea. / ……给那些无法独立生存的青蛙和蟾蜍设立保护区？这主意不错。\"(break)speak Sebastian \"He does look pretty tough. But still, If I find another injured frog, I think he'd be better off with a friend.\"/faceDirection farmer 1/pause 1200/quickQuestion #Why do you like frogs so much, anyway?#I don't really want this in the house#I'm glad you've found a new hobby(break)speak Sebastian \"Hmm... Well, I like going out in the rain. So I guess I encountered a lot of frogs that way. / 嗯……我喜欢在雨中外出。所以我觉得我遇到过很多这样的青蛙。#$b#I ended up feeling a common bond with the little guys. / 我最终感觉到了和这帮小家伙的共同纽带。\"\\faceDirection farmer 1 true\\emote farmer 20(break)emote Sebastian 12\\showFrame Sebastian 12\\pause 400\\speak Sebastian \"Well it's not up for debate. This is my corner of the house and I can do what I want with it.\"\\showFrame Sebastian 0(break)speak Sebastian \"Yeah, it'll be fun. I spend a lot of time on the computer, so it's nice to have some real, physical hobbies.#$b#I might even try my hand at some frog breeding!$h\"\\faceDirection farmer 1 true\\emote farmer 16\\pause 500/faceDirection farmer 2/showFrame farmer 0/pause 1000/playSound croak/specificTemporarySprite frogJump/pause 250/playSound slimeHit/pause 250/showFrame farmer 94/jump Sebastian/pause 250/playSound slimeHit/pause 500/playSound slimeHit/pause 250/fade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 600/message \"Today our family grew a little larger... / 今天我们有了新的家庭成员……\"/pause 1000/playSound slimeHit/pause 500/playSound slimeHit/pause 500/playSound slimeHit/pause 1000/message \"...and a lot slimier! / ……并且更黏糊了！\"/pause 1000/end"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Events/FishShop",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "16253595/j 29/X": "distantBanjo/6 6/farmer 5 9 0 Willy -100 -100 2/skippable/move farmer 0 -1 0/pause 1000/warp Willy 4 4/playsound doorClose/pause 100/textAboveHead Willy \"Ahoy! / 啊嘿！\"/pause 500/move Willy 1 0 2/speak Willy \"Come in... make yourself at home... / 进来吧……别客气……\"/move farmer 0 -1 0/move farmer -1 0 3/pause 1000/animate farmer true true 9999 35/playSound quickSlosh/pause 800/playSound quickSlosh/pause 800/speak Willy \"Aye... that's good stuff, there. The fish go crazy for it. / 啊……这可是好东西，鱼儿们肯定超爱这个。#$b#Just... eh... make sure to wash yer hands good after dipping them in those juices...$s / 就是……呃……用手碰过这些汁液之后一定要洗手……$s\"/speak Willy \"The aroma has been known to linger for up to seven weeks, ${lad^miss}$... / 据说这种气味可以持续不散七个星期，${小伙子^小姑娘}$……\"/stopAnimation farmer/startJittering/jump farmer/positionOffset farmer 4 0/pause 50/positionOffset farmer 4 0/pause 50/positionOffset farmer 4 0/pause 50/positionOffset farmer 4 0/pause 50/positionOffset farmer 4 0/pause 50/positionOffset farmer 4 0/pause 50/positionOffset farmer 4 0/pause 50/positionOffset farmer 4 0/pause 50/stopJittering/pause 1000/speak Willy \"So... you been catching a lot o' fish? / 所以说……你钓了很多鱼上来？\"/pause 300/stopAnimation farmer/faceDirection farmer 0/pause 500/quickQuestion #Yes#No#It's too difficult...(break)emote Willy 20\\speak Willy \"Aha! A ${man^lady}$ after me own heart...$h / 啊哈！一位跟我志同道合的小${伙子^姑娘}$……$h\"\\pause 500\\speak Willy \"You can always ${trust a fisherman^count on a lady who fishes}$...\"\\speak Willy \"That's what me ol' Pappy used to say, at least. Haha!$h#$b#Well, keep it goin'... if you can catch every fish in these waters, I've got a special prize waitin' for ye...\"(break)emote Willy 28\\speak Willy \"Not the fishin' type, eh? That's too bad...$s\"(break)emote Willy 16\\speak Willy \"Yes, it's a difficult sport... especially for a beginner.#$b#Have you tried the 'Training Rod'? I sell them right here, at a very low price.#$b#You should try using a 'Training Rod' until you get a little more experienced.\"/pause 1500/faceDirection Willy 3/emote Willy 28/quickQuestion #What's wrong?#Everything okay?(break)pause 100(break)pause 100/pause 400/speak Willy \"Aye... well, business has been tough, lately.$s / 嗯……最近生意不太好做。$s#$b#It all started about the same time that old community center fell to ruin... me fish just don't sell like they used to... / 自从旧的社区中心关闭之后，我的鱼就卖的没以前好了……#$b#I've been working double-time just to make ends meet! / 为了养家糊口，我得花两倍的时间工作！\"/faceDirection Willy 2/pause 300/speak Willy \"No time for me own projects...$s / 没时间做我自己的事了……$s#$b#But, if things picked back up around here, I might have the time to show ya somethin'... / 但是，如果这里的情况好转，我可能会有时间给你看一些东西……\"/move Willy -1 0 0/playMusic none/speak Willy \"Heh heh... yep. She's back there... an 'old friend' that's seen better days...$h / 呵呵……是的。它就在那后面……是一位“老朋友”，跟我经历过快乐的时光……$h\"/pause 500/emote farmer 8/pause 1000/playMusic ocean/playSound shwip/faceDirection Willy 1 true/pause 40/faceDirection Willy 2/speak Willy \"Some day, ${lad^miss}$... you'll see what I mean. / 总有一天，${小伙子^小姑娘}$……你会明白的……\"/pause 2000/end"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Events/Forest",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "3910979/f Vincent 2000/f Jas 2000/t 600 1700/z summer/z fall/z winter/w sunny": "playful/-2000 -2000/farmer 84 32 2 Jas 85 39 3 Vincent 83 39 1/skippable/specificTemporarySprite springOnion/move farmer 0 5 2 true/viewport 84 39 true/move false/faceDirection Vincent 0/faceDirection Jas 0/jump Vincent/pause 1000/faceDirection Jas 3/speak Vincent \"Hiya, mister @! / 嗨，@先生！^Hiya, miss @! / 嗨，@小姐！\"/pause 500/emote farmer 8/faceDirection Vincent 1/move farmer 0 1 2/jump Vincent/pause 1000/speak Vincent \"Sp..spwing onion. Mom sends me out to pick these sometimes... / 圭……菁葱。妈妈有时候会派我出去采摘这些……\"/pause 100/faceDirection Jas 0/speak Jas \"They're too spicy for me!$s / 他们对我来说太辣了！$s\"/faceDirection Jas 3/emote farmer 28/jump Vincent/faceDirection Vincent 0 true/pause 90/faceDirection Vincent 3 true/pause 90/faceDirection Vincent 2 true/pause 90/faceDirection Vincent 1 true/pause 90/faceDirection Vincent 0/pause 500/playMusic spring_day_ambient/speak Vincent \"You're really nice for a grown-up... so I'm going to show you a secret.$h / 就成年人来说，你真的很好，所以我会告诉你一个秘密。$h\"/pause 1000/playMusic distantBanjo/fade/viewport -2000 -2000/viewport -1000 -1000 true/specificTemporarySprite springOnionDemo/pause 5000/speak Vincent \"When you see it like this, it looks good, right? / 当你这样看时，它看起来没异样吧？是吧？\"/pause 3000/speak Vincent \"But if you peel it a little bit... / 但是如果你稍微剥开一点……\"/pause 500/playSound harvest/specificTemporarySprite springOnionPeel/pause 3000/speak Vincent \"...It's full of bugs!$s / ……里面全是虫子！$s\"/pause 2500/specificTemporarySprite springOnionRemove/viewport 84 39 true/playMusic spring_day_ambient/pause 2000/speak Vincent \"Cool, huh?$h / 酷吧，嗯？$h\"/faceDirection Vincent 1/speak Jas \"Um... What do you do with the bugs, Vincent? / 嗯……文森特，你如何处理这些虫子？\"/jump Vincent/pause 800/speak Vincent \"Usually I just squash 'em! / 通常我就挤死他们！\"/pause 500/shake Jas 2000/jump Jas/textAboveHead Jas \"*gasp*! / *喘气*！\"/pause 2000/speak Jas \"That's horrible! No, no, no, no, no...$s / 太恐怖了！不要……要……$s\"/faceDirection Jas 0/speak Jas \"Mr. @? Please... put the bugs back in the grass so they can live in peace. / @ 先生？请……把虫子放回草地，让它们能够安定地生活。^Miss @? Please... put the bugs back in the grass so they can live in peace. / @ 小姐？请……把虫子放回草地，让它们能够安定地生活。\"/emote farmer 40/animate farmer false true 200 102 103/speed Vincent 4/move Vincent -1 0 2/speed Vincent 4/move Vincent 0 1 1/speed Vincent 4/move Vincent 1 0 0/speed Vincent 4/move Vincent 0 -1 0/speed Vincent 4/move Vincent -1 0 2/speed Vincent 4/move Vincent 0 1 1/speed Vincent 4/move Vincent 1 0 0/speed Vincent 4/move Vincent 0 -1 0/jump Vincent/fade/viewport -3000 -3000/pause 1000/message \"You learned how to clean the spring onion... without harming any bugs. / 你学会了如何清理青葱，且不伤害任何虫子。\"/pause 1000/playSound reward/message \"Spring onions are now worth 5x the gold! / 青葱现在值 5 倍金子！\"/pause 1000/end",
        "611944/f Shane 500/t 2000 2400": "nightTime/-1000 -1000/farmer 33 18 2 Shane 34 25 2/skippable/addLantern 735 35 25 1/animate Shane false true 200 20 20 20 20 20 20 20 20 20 20 21 22 23 24 24 24 24 23 22 21 20 20 20 20/viewport 34 25 true/move farmer 0 7 2/pause 2000/speak Shane \"Up late, huh? / 已经很晚了哈？\"/stopAnimation Shane/showFrame Shane 20/pause 1000/speak Shane \"Here, have a cold one. / 给，来杯凉的。\"/pause 500/showFrame Shane 25/pause 1000/playSound coin/showFrame 90/stopAnimation Shane/showFrame Shane 20/pause 5000/showFrame Shane 20/speak Shane \"Buh... Life. / 生活啊。\"/playMusic echos/pause 4000/speak Shane \"You ever feel like... no matter what you do, you're gonna fail? / 你有没有这种感觉……无论你做什么都会失败？#$b#...Like you're stuck in some miserable abyss and you're so deep you can't even see the light of day? / 就好像你陷入痛苦的深渊无法自拔，看不到一点光芒？\"/pause 2000/speak Shane \"I just feel like no matter how hard I try... I'm not strong enough to climb out of that hole. / 我感觉不管我多努力……我都无法强大到从那个洞里爬出来。\"/pause 3000/farmerEat 346/pause 4000/speak Shane \"Heh... fast drinker, huh? Man after my own heart. / 喝挺快啊？是个我欣赏的汉子。^Heh... fast drinker, huh? Woman after my own heart. / 喝挺快啊？是个我欣赏的姑娘。#$b#Just don't make it a habit... you got a future ahead of you still. / 不过别上瘾了……你还有大好年华呢。\"/pause 3000/stopAnimation Shane/showFrame Shane 19/speak Shane \"Welp.. My liver's beggin' me to stop. Better call it a night. / 哎哟……我的肝已经给我发警报了。那就晚安了。#$b#See you around, @. / 回头见，@。\"/move Shane 0 -6 0 true/pause 1000/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/end",
        "3091462/e 3911124/O Leah/w sunny/t 1130 1400/A leahPaint": "breezy/-1000 -1000/farmer 75 40 3 Leah 73 38 3 Marnie 70 39 1/skippable/specificTemporarySprite leahPaintingSetup/animate farmer true true 100 80 80 80 80 81 81 81 81 80 80 80 80 81 81 81 81 81 81 81 81 81 81 81 81 81 81/makeInvisible 68 36 13 7/animate Leah false true 100 48 49 48 49 48 49 48 49 48 48 48 48 48 48 48 48 48 49 48 49 48 48 48 48 48 48/viewport 72 39 true/pause 6000/emote Marnie 28/speak Marnie \"Um... Leah? How much longer will this be?$s / 唔……利亚？还要多久？$s#$b#...My knees are quivering, my thighs are whimpering, and I've lost all sensation in my foot.$s / ……我的膝盖在颤抖，我的大腿在哭泣，我的脚已经失去了知觉。 $s\"/shake Marnie 500/pause 1000/shake Marnie 500/speak Leah \"Just keep perfectly still, Marnie... No squirming!$h / 只要保持完全静止就好，玛妮……不要动！$h\"/emote Marnie 28/speak Leah \"Hey, @... what style do you think I should do? I'm up for anything... / 嘿，@……你觉得我应该画什么风格？我什么都行……\"/pause 1000/quickQuestion #Classic country portrait#Colorful, retro pop-art#Minimalist modern(break)speak Leah \"Stick with the classic look, huh? Yeah, I think Marnie will appreciate that. / 保持传统风格是吗？好的，我想玛妮会喜欢的。\"\\addWorldState m_painting0(break)speak Leah \"Good idea! That sounds fun... Let me get some more yellow paint on the palette...\"\\addWorldState m_painting1(break)speak Leah \"Hmm... not my usual style, but I'll give it a shot. I'd better switch to acrylic paint for this one...\"\\addWorldState m_painting2/pause 500/speak Leah \"How's yours coming along? / 你的怎么样了？\"/quickQuestion #It's a masterpiece of fine art!#I'm trying my best...#It looks like chicken scratch(break)speak Leah \"Wow, I like your confidence!$h / 哇，我喜欢你的自信！$h#$b#Who knows? Maybe you'll become the next Lupini!$h / 谁说得准呢？也许你就是下一个卢皮尼呢！$h#$b#...Can't wait to see it. / ……我都等不及要看了。\"(break)speak Leah \"Hey, that's all I ask. If you keep trying your best you can't help but get better at it!\"(break)speak Leah \"Hey, that's okay! You gotta start somewhere. And you never know, one person's chicken scratch is another person's 'modern art'.\"/pause 500/textAboveHead Marnie \"Make me look good! / 把我画得漂亮一点！\"/pause 1500/textAboveHead Leah \"Shh! / 嘘！\"/pause 2300/speak Leah \"Now, don't forget the techniques I taught you... broad strokes, hold the brush like so... / 好了，别忘了我教你的技巧……线条要粗，这样握画笔……\"/pause 1000/playSound slimeHit/pause 1000/playSound slimeHit/pause 1000/playSound slimeHit/pause 2000/stopAnimation Leah/showFrame Leah 12/textAboveHead Leah \"There! / 好了！\"/pause 3000/faceDirection Leah 2 true/playSound coin/specificTemporarySprite leahHoldPainting/pause 1000/textAboveHead Leah \"What do you think? / 你看看如何？\"/pause 2000/textAboveHead Marnie \"Oooh! / 哦哦哦！\"/emote farmer 56/pause 2000/specificTemporarySprite leahStopHoldingPainting/pause 1000/speak Marnie \"I love it! That's going up in my room...$h / 我超喜欢！我要把它挂在我的房间里……$h\"/pause 500/speak Leah \"Now, let's see what you've got, @. / 好了，让我们看看你的怎么样，@。\"/specificTemporarySprite removeSprite 444/stopAnimation farmer/faceDirection farmer 3/move Leah 4 0 2/move Leah 0 1 3/pause 100/showFrame Leah 24/pause 1000/showFrame Leah 12/emote Leah 40/emote Leah 28/speak Leah \"Erm... It's... interesting!$6 / 呃……这……很有趣！$6#$b#It's, uh... a different kind of approach, for sure...$6 / 肯定是用了，呃……一种不同的方法……$6\"/pause 500/emote Marnie 8/move Marnie 0 2 1/textAboveHead Marnie \"Let me see / 让我看看\"/move Marnie 7 0 0/move Marnie 0 -1 3/pause 500/emote Marnie 8/pause 1000/faceDirection farmer 2 true/playSound coin/showFrame farmer 57/specificTemporarySprite farmerHoldPainting/pause 500/showFrame Marnie 16/pause 50/jump Marnie/shake Marnie 3000/faceDirection Leah 2/pause 2000/speak Leah \"Marnie, you can hang both of these in your room!$h / 玛妮，你可以把两幅都挂在你的房间！$h\"/jump Marnie/pause 1500/speak Marnie \"Em... @, why don't you go ahead and keep yours? It might be nice to, uh... own your first-ever painting... ya know?$s / 呃……@，要不你把自己的画留下来吧？把自己的第一幅画收藏起来，呃……很棒的……是吧？$s\"/pause 1000/awardFestivalPrize marniePainting/pause 2000/fade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 500/end dialogue Leah \"Um... Honey? Where were you planning to hang that painting you did?$3\"",
        "14/f Haley 2000/z winter/t 1000 1600/w sunny": "spring_day_ambient/100 23/farmer 94 23 1 Haley 100 23 1/skippable/pause 2000/showFrame Haley 25/pause 500/playSound cameraNoise/shake Haley 50/screenFlash .5/pause 800/pause 500/faceDirection Haley 2 true/showFrame Haley 24/pause 500/playSound cameraNoise/shake Haley 50/screenFlash .5/move farmer 5 0 1 true/pause 1200/faceDirection Haley 3 true/showFrame Haley 27/pause 400/jump Haley/pause 600/showFrame Haley 12/faceDirection Haley 3/pause 300/speak Haley \"Oh! @.$8 / 噢！@。$8\"/pause 500/faceDirection Haley 2/pause 800/speak Haley \"The lighting is so nice right now... I had to come out and take some nature shots. / 阳光真好……我出来拍拍照片。\"/pause 600/faceDirection Haley 3/pause 600/faceDirection Haley 3/pause 400/speak Haley \"I've been trying to connect with the outdoors a little more... / 我想多出门走走……#$b#I wanna know what it's like, being a farmer. It's a way of life I've never really thought about. / 我想知道农民生活是什么样的。我从没想过这样的生活。#$b#Well, until now...$l / 直到现在……$l\"/pause 500/faceDirection Haley 0/pause 800/speak Haley \"Heh, these cows are so cute... / 呵呵，这些奶牛好可爱……\"/pause 600/emote Haley 16/faceDirection Haley 3/speak Haley \"Hey, I have an idea!$h / 嘿，我有个主意！$h\"/move Haley 0 1 2/faceDirection farmer 2/playSound sandyStep/addBigProp 100 25 106/pause 600/move Haley 0 -1 3/faceDirection farmer 1/speak Haley \"Let's take some pictures with these cows! You can show me how to approach one.$h / 我们跟这些奶牛合张影吧！你教教我怎么接近奶牛！$h#$b#I'll just set it to shoot on a timer. / 我会设置好定时器。\"/move Haley 0 1 2/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 900/playSound openBox/move Haley 0 -1 3/faceDirection farmer 1/pause 700/faceDirection farmer 0/faceDirection Haley 0/playMusic 50s/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/cutscene haleyCows/pause 2000/speak Haley \"...geh...$9 / 哞……$9\"/pause 1000/speak Haley \"*giggle*$10 / * 咯咯 *$10#$b#That was fun, @! ...And these photos are hilarious!$10 / 太好玩了，@！这些照片也很滑稽！$10\"/pause 500/speak Haley \"I'm gonna go home and take a shower now...$10 / 我现在想要回家洗个澡……$10\"/pause 1000/mail haleyGarden/end dialogue Haley \"Well, that was the dirtiest I've ever been.$h\"",
        "fieldTripEnd": "pause 400/emote Penny 40/speak Penny \"Well, that's probably enough for today. You two run along and play. / 嗯，今天差不多就这样吧。你俩去玩吧。\"/speed Jas 4/move Jas 0 3 1/speed Jas 4/move Jas 9 0 3 true/faceDirection Vincent 2 true/jump Vincent/pause 800/speed Vincent 4/move Vincent 0 3 1 false/speed Vincent 4/move Vincent 9 0 1/pause 500/faceDirection Vincent 2/faceDirection Jas 2/faceDirection Penny 1/faceDirection farmer 3/speak Penny \"It's a lot of work to take care of these kids...$u / 照顾这些孩子很累……$u#$b#But I don't really mind. I enjoy seeing them learn... and hopefully I can help them grow up to be good people. / 但我不介意。我喜欢看着他们学习……我也希望能帮他们成长为优秀的人。\"/faceDirection Penny 2/pause 500/faceDirection Penny 1/speak Penny \"$q -1 null#Would you ever want to be a parent, @? / 你想过要孩子吗，@？#$r -1 0 event_speaker_kids1#I haven't really thought about it. / 我还没认真想过。#$r -1 20 event_speaker_kids2#Absolutely. I want a big family. / 那当然，我想要很多孩子。#$r -1 20 event_speaker_kids3#I guess so. It's a natural urge. / 有吧，这是人的本能愿望。#$r -1 10 event_speaker_kids4#No, I don't think I'd be good at it. / 没有，我觉得我不适合。#$r -1 -10 event_speaker_kids5#No, the world's crowded enough already. / 不想，这个世界的人已经够多了。#$r -1 -10 event_speaker_kids6#No, I don't want to be tied down with a family. / 不想，我不想被家庭束缚。\"/viewport move 1 0 10000/pause 7000/stopMusic/globalFade/viewport -2000 -2000/speak Penny \"Well, I'm glad you showed up, @. I think the kids had a great time.$h / 那好吧，我很高兴你能来，@。孩子们玩得很开心。$h\"/end dialogue Penny \"Thanks for making my field trip a success today.\"",
        "eventEnd": "faceDirection Penny 3/emote Penny 12/end dialogue Penny \"I can't believe you refused to help me out.$a\"",
        "54/f Leah 2500/t 1100 1600/z winter/w sunny": "50s/-1000 -1000/farmer 87 40 3 Leah 76 40 1/skippable/specificTemporarySprite leahPicnic/viewport 77 40 true/move farmer -10 0 3/speak Leah \"Hi @. I knew you'd be passing through here today. / 嗨，@。我知道你今天会从这路过。#$b#...So I put together a surprise...$h / ……所以我准备了个惊喜……$h\"/faceDirection Leah 0/pause 800/speak Leah \"It's a little picnic for us!$h / 一起小小地野餐一顿吧！$h\"/pause 500/faceDirection Leah 1/pause 500/faceDirection Leah 0/speak Leah \"This is a vegetable medley, with my 'special' spice blend. / 这是蔬菜杂烩，用我“特制”的调味品调制的。\"/pause 600/move Leah -1 0 0/speak Leah \"...and this is a fresh salad, made from greens that I foraged right here in the forest!$h / ……这是新鲜的沙拉，用的是我从这座森林里采来的蔬菜！$h\"/pause 600/faceDirection Leah 1/move farmer -1 0 3/faceDirection Leah 0/pause 1200/speak Leah \"@, um...$l / @，呃……$l\"/faceDirection Leah 2/pause 300/faceDirection Leah 1/speak Leah \"I just want to say thank you... for helping me get one step closer to becoming a real artist.$l / 我想谢谢你……帮助我距离成为真正的艺术家又近了一步。$l\"/pause 400/showFrame Leah 25/pause 100/positionOffset Leah 2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Leah 2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Leah 2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Leah 2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Leah 2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Leah 2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Leah 2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Leah 2 0/pause 50/animate farmer true true 100 101/positionOffset farmer 16 0/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 50/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 50/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 50/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 50/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 50/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 50/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 50/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 500/specificTemporarySprite heart 76 39/pause 1000/stopMusic/message \"DISTANT VOICE: Well, well, well... What have we here? / 遥远的声音：哎呀哎呀哎呀……看看谁来了？\"/warp LeahEx 74 29/move LeahEx 0 9 2 true/stopAnimation farmer/positionOffset farmer -16 0/faceDirection farmer 0 true/showFrame Leah 4/pause 50/positionOffset Leah -4 0/positionOffset farmer 4 0/pause 50/positionOffset Leah -4 0/positionOffset farmer 4 0/pause 50/positionOffset Leah -4 0/positionOffset farmer 4 0/pause 50/positionOffset Leah -4 0/positionOffset farmer 4 0/faceDirection Leah 0/pause 4000/showFrame LeahEx 4/move Leah -1 0 0/speak Leah \"Kel??$6 / 凯尔？？$6#$b#What the heck are you doing here?$a / 你怎么在这儿？$a\"/fork LeahInternet choseInternet/message \"KEL: Didn't you see me at the art show? I came all the way from Zuzu City to see your sculptures. / 凯尔：你在艺术展上没看见我吗？我大老远从祖祖城跑来看你的雕像。\"/move LeahEx 0 1 2/message \"KEL: And to get you to come back with me. / 凯尔：还有让你和我一起回去。\"/message \"KEL: I want things to go back to the way they were... I miss you, babe. / 凯尔：我想回到从前……我想你，宝贝。\"/emote Leah 12/faceDirection Leah 0/speak Leah \"Yuck, don't call me that!$a / 呸，少肉麻！$a#$b#You never supported my art before... now that I've had some success you want me back? You make me sick.$a / 你以前从来不支持我的艺术……现在我成功了，你就浪子回头了？真恶心。$a\"/move Leah 0 2 2/showFrame LeahEx 4/message \"KEL: Hey! Come Here! / 凯尔：嘿！过来！\"/speed farmer 4/move farmer -2 0 0 false/question fork1 \"#Punch Kel in the face.#Try reasoning with Kel. / #朝凯尔脸上打一拳。#去跟凯尔讲道理。\"/fork noPunch/pause 300/screenFlash .25/animate farmer false false 650 15/positionOffset farmer 0 -8/faceDirection Leah 0 true/playSound clubhit/showFrame LeahEx 6/jump LeahEx/positionOffset LeahEx 0 -4/pause 25/positionOffset LeahEx 0 -4/pause 25/positionOffset farmer 0 8/positionOffset LeahEx 0 -4/pause 25/positionOffset LeahEx 0 -4/pause 25/positionOffset LeahEx 0 -4/pause 25/positionOffset LeahEx 0 -4/pause 25/positionOffset LeahEx 0 -4/pause 25/positionOffset LeahEx 0 -4/pause 25/positionOffset LeahEx 0 -4/pause 25/pause 200/playSound clubSmash/showFrame LeahEx 7/shake LeahEx 1000/speak Leah \"Oh my God!$6 / 我的天啊！$6\"/speed Leah 4/move Leah -1 0 0/speed Leah 4/move Leah 0 -4 1/emote Leah 40/pause 1700/speak Leah \"Well, he'll make it... but that was pretty violent, @. / 他没事的……但还真是暴力。@。^She's fine... but that was pretty violent, @. / 她没事的……但还真是暴力。@。\"/faceDirection Leah 2/speak Leah \"Let's get out of here. I don't think Kel will be bothering us anymore. / 我们走吧凯尔不会再打扰我们了。\"/speed farmer 2/positionOffset farmer 2 0/move farmer -1 0 0/move Leah 0 -8 0 true/move farmer 0 -8 0 true/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 1000/speak Leah \"Let's find a more secluded spot this time...$l / 这次找个更僻静的地方吧……$l\"/playMusic none/pause 2000/end dialogue Leah \"Well, the picnic didn't pan out like I wanted it to.$h\"",
        "choseMinerals": "pause 500/animate Vincent false true 50 16 17/playSound dwop/pause 300/faceDirection Penny 2/pause 500/stopAnimation Vincent/speak Penny \"Yes, Vincent? / 文森特？\"/speak Vincent \"Farmer @? Is it true that goblins live deep in the caves... and that they like to kidnap little girls for their dinner? / @？山洞真的住着哥布林吗……它们真的会吃小孩吗？\"/jump Jas/pause 800/faceDirection Jas 3/emote Jas 28/animate farmer false true 100 102 103/speak Penny \"Vincent! You're scaring Jas. Let's not talk about monsters.$a / 文森特！你吓到贾斯了。我们别聊怪物的事情了。$a\"/faceDirection Penny 1/faceDirection Jas 0/emote Penny 12/pause 400/stopAnimation farmer/pause 300/faceDirection farmer 3/emote farmer 40/faceDirection Penny 2/faceDirection farmer 2/switchEvent fieldTripEnd",
        "52/f Leah 1500/p Leah/z winter": "playful/-1000 -1000/farmer 58 16 3 Leah 42 11 3/skippable/specificTemporarySprite leahTree/animate Leah false true 80 22 23 22 23 22 23 22 23 21 21 21 21 21 21/viewport 40 10 true/move farmer -7 0 2/move farmer 0 -4 3/move farmer -3 0 3/jump Leah/move farmer -5 0 3/jump Leah/move farmer 0 -1 3/stopAnimation Leah/pause 600/faceDirection Leah 1/speak Leah \"Oh! @! You scared me.$6 / 噢！@！你吓到我了！$6\"/pause 430/faceDirection Leah 3/showFrame Leah 21/speak Leah \"See that fruit up there? It looks delicious, doesn't it? / 看见上面的水果了吗？看起来很好吃啊！#$b#But I can't reach it.$s / 可是我够不到。$s\"/pause 500/emote farmer 40/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 3/animate farmer true false 150 58 59 60 61 61 61 61/showFrame Leah 24/playSound pickUpItem/positionOffset Leah 4 -8/pause 25/positionOffset Leah 4 -8/pause 25/positionOffset Leah 4 -8/pause 25/positionOffset Leah 4 -8/pause 25/positionOffset Leah 4 -8/pause 25/positionOffset Leah 4 -8/pause 25/positionOffset Leah 4 -8/pause 25/positionOffset Leah 4 -8/pause 25/positionOffset Leah 4 -8/pause 25/positionOffset Leah 4 -8/pause 25/positionOffset Leah 4 -4/pause 25/positionOffset Leah 4 -4/pause 25/positionOffset Leah 4 -4/pause 25/positionOffset Leah 4 -4/pause 25/positionOffset Leah 4 -4/pause 25/positionOffset Leah 4 -4/pause 25/stopAnimation farmer/animate farmer true true 100 61/shake Leah 1000/pause 250/speak Leah \"Aghh!$6 / 啊啊！$6#$b#Hehe...Thanks.$h / 呵呵……谢了。$h\"/showFrame Leah 21/pause 850/animate Leah false true 60 22 23/speak Leah \"Okay... got it! / 好的……拿到了！\"/jump Leah/removeSprite 42 8/playSound coin/pause 950/stopAnimation Leah/showFrame Leah 24/stopAnimation farmer/animate farmer true false 150 61 60 59 58 58 58 58 58/positionOffset Leah -4 8/pause 25/positionOffset Leah -4 8/pause 25/positionOffset Leah -4 8/pause 25/positionOffset Leah -4 8/pause 25/positionOffset Leah -4 8/pause 25/positionOffset Leah -4 8/pause 25/positionOffset Leah -4 8/pause 25/positionOffset Leah -4 8/pause 25/positionOffset Leah -4 8/pause 25/positionOffset Leah -4 8/pause 25/positionOffset Leah -4 4/pause 25/positionOffset Leah -4 4/pause 25/positionOffset Leah -4 4/pause 25/positionOffset Leah -4 4/pause 25/positionOffset Leah -4 4/pause 25/positionOffset Leah -4 4/pause 25/faceDirection Leah 1 true/stopAnimation farmer/faceDirection farmer 3/pause 500/speak Leah \"You're stronger than you look!$h / 你比看起来还要强壮！$h\"/pause 1000/speak Leah \"Here, try a piece...  / 给，尝一块……\"/pause 300/farmerEat 613/pause 900/pause 1100/stopAnimation farmer/faceDirection farmer 2/viewport move -1 1 6000/pause 2000/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 1000/playMusic none/speak Leah \"You know, I just realized something. / 我刚想起来一件事。#$b#Even if my art career is a flop, I'll always have a friend to catch me on the way down.$h / 就算我的艺术生涯以失败告终，也总会有朋友在我跌落谷底的过程中捞我一把。$h\"/pause 1000/end dialogue Leah \"Thanks for helping me earlier...$h\"",
        "318560/j 10/t 900 1600/d Tue Wed Fri Sat": "communityCenter/94 99/farmer 98 88 2 Jas 95 100 3 Vincent 93 100 1/playMusic communityCenter/skippable/move farmer 0 6 2 true/pause 1000/speak Jas \"Ew... it smells.$s / 呃……好难闻。$s\"/pause 600/jump Vincent/pause 500/faceDirection Vincent 0/pause 500/showFrame Vincent 16/shake Vincent 400/playSound clank/pause 800/shake Vincent 400/playSound clank/pause 800/showFrame Vincent 8/speak Vincent \"...$s / ……$s#$b#Why is it locked? I wanna explore the sewers!$s / 怎么锁上了？我还想去下水道里探索一番呢！$s\"/pause 800/faceDirection Jas 0/pause 800/speak Jas \"I think Gunther has the key. / 钥匙应该在冈瑟手里。\"/pause 300/faceDirection Vincent 1/speak Vincent \"Professor Gunther? The man who runs the museum? Why do you think he has it?$u / 冈瑟教授？开博物馆的那个？你为什么会觉得钥匙在他手里？$u\"/pause 500/faceDirection Jas 3/speak Jas \"I saw a big rusty old key fall out of his pocket one time. / 有一次，我见到一把生锈的大钥匙从他的口袋里掉了出来。#$b#A creepy sewer door like this has just got to be a match for a big rusty old key.$4 / 这种瘆人的下水道大门一定得配一把生锈的旧钥匙。$4\"/playMusic none/pause 2000/playSound slimeHit/pause 400/playSound slimeHit/pause 400/playSound slimeHit/pause 500/emote Vincent 8 true/emote Jas 8 true/pause 900/faceDirection Vincent 0 true/faceDirection Jas 0 true/pause 1600/playSound shadowpeep/shake Vincent 5000/shake Jas 5000/jump Jas/jump Vincent/faceDirection farmer 3 true/faceDirection Vincent 0 true/faceDirection Jas 0 true/pause 1500/playSound shadowDie/jump Vincent/jump Jas/pause 800/speed Vincent 6/speed Jas 6/advancedMove Jas false 4 0 0 -7 -1 0/advancedMove Vincent false 6 0 0 -8 -1 0/proceedPosition Vincent 98 92/faceDirection farmer 0 true/faceDirection Jas 2 true/faceDirection Vincent 2 true/speak Jas \"There's something moving around in there!$u / 里面有东西在动！$u\"/shake Jas 4000/shake Vincent 4000/pause 1000/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 1000/move farmer 0 6 3 false/move farmer -4 0 0/pause 800/emote farmer 40/pause 1600/playSound shadowpeep/faceDirection farmer 2 true/jump farmer/showFrame 94/jump Vincent/jump Jas/speed Jas 4/speed Vincent 4/move Jas 0 -6 0 true/move Vincent 0 -6 0 true/pause 1000/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/end",
        "noPunch": "pause 10/message \"KEL: I have nothing to say to you. Get out of my way. / 凯尔：我跟你没什么好说的。给我滚开。\"/speed farmer 2/move farmer 1 0 3/move LeahEx 0 2 2/message \"KEL: Seriously, Leah... What are you doing out here with this simple-minded bumpkin? / 凯尔：说真的，莉亚……你和这个头脑简单的乡巴佬在这里干什么呢？\"/faceDirection farmer 2/showFrame Leah 26/pause 1000/showFrame Leah 27/showFrame 94/playSound clubhit/screenFlash .25/showFrame LeahEx 6/jump LeahEx/positionOffset LeahEx 0 -4/pause 25/positionOffset LeahEx 0 -4/pause 25/positionOffset farmer 0 8/positionOffset LeahEx 0 -4/pause 25/positionOffset LeahEx 0 -4/pause 25/positionOffset LeahEx 0 -4/pause 25/positionOffset LeahEx 0 -4/pause 25/positionOffset LeahEx 0 -4/pause 25/positionOffset LeahEx 0 -4/pause 25/positionOffset LeahEx 0 -4/pause 25/pause 200/playSound clubSmash/showFrame LeahEx 7/shake LeahEx 1000/stopAnimation farmer/speak Leah \"@'s a better ${man^person}$ than you in every respect!$a / @${的各个方面都比你强多了^从各方面来看都比你优秀得多}$！$a#$b#Now get out of here and never come back!$a / 你赶紧滚吧，不要再回来了！$a\"/move Leah -1 0 0/move Leah 0 -4 1/speak Leah \"Let's go, @. I don't think Kel will be bothering us anymore. / 走吧。@。凯尔不会再打扰我们了。\"/move farmer 0 1 2/faceDirection Leah 2 true/move farmer -2 0 0/move Leah 0 -11 0 true/move farmer 0 -11 0 true/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 1000/speak Leah \"Let's find a more secluded spot this time...$l / 这次找个更僻静的地方吧……$l\"/playMusic none/pause 2000/end dialogue Leah \"Well, the picnic didn't pan out like I wanted it to.$h\"",
        "choseInternet": "pause 10/message \"KEL: I found your online art store... weren't you wondering about the 'Mr. K' who kept buying all your sculptures? / 凯尔：我找到了你的网上艺术商店……你就不好奇一直买你雕像的“K 先生”吗？\"/pause 90/speak Leah \"You're 'Mr. K'? I... I thought it was just a rich guy who truly loved my art.$s / 你就是“K 先生”？我……我以为就是以为喜欢我的艺术的富豪呢。$s\"/move LeahEx 0 1 2/message \"KEL: Heh. Well, you were half right... / 凯尔：嘿嘿。你猜对了一半……\"/pause 1000/message \"KEL: Look, Leah. I want you back. I miss you, babe. / 凯尔：莉亚，我想让你回到我身边。我想你，宝贝。\"/emote Leah 12/faceDirection Leah 0/speak Leah \"Ew, don't call me that!$a / 咦，少肉麻了！$a#$b#You never supported my art before... now that I've had some success you want me back? You make me sick.$a / 你以前从来不支持我的艺术……现在我成功了，你就浪子回头了？真恶心。$a\"/move Leah 0 2 2/showFrame LeahEx 4/message \"KEL: Hey! Come Here! / 凯尔：嘿！过来！\"/speed farmer 4/move farmer -2 0 0 false/question fork1 \"#Punch Kel in the face.#Try reasoning with Kel. / #朝凯尔脸上打一拳。#和凯尔理论。\"/fork noPunch/pause 300/screenFlash .25/animate farmer false false 650 15/positionOffset farmer 0 -8/faceDirection Leah 0 true/playSound clubhit/showFrame LeahEx 6/jump LeahEx/positionOffset LeahEx 0 -4/pause 25/positionOffset LeahEx 0 -4/pause 25/positionOffset farmer 0 8/positionOffset LeahEx 0 -4/pause 25/positionOffset LeahEx 0 -4/pause 25/positionOffset LeahEx 0 -4/pause 25/positionOffset LeahEx 0 -4/pause 25/positionOffset LeahEx 0 -4/pause 25/positionOffset LeahEx 0 -4/pause 25/positionOffset LeahEx 0 -4/pause 25/pause 200/playSound clubSmash/showFrame LeahEx 7/shake LeahEx 1000/speak Leah \"Oh my God!$6 / 我的天啊！$6\"/speed Leah 4/move Leah -1 0 0/speed Leah 4/move Leah 0 -4 1/emote Leah 40/pause 1700/speak Leah \"Well, he's fine... but that was pretty violent, @. / 他没事的……但还真是暴力，@。^She's fine... but that was pretty violent, @. / 她没事的……但还真是暴力，@。\"/faceDirection Leah 2/speak Leah \"Let's get out of here. I don't think Kel will be bothering us anymore. / 我们走吧。凯尔不会再打扰我们了。\"/speed farmer 2/positionOffset farmer 2 0/move farmer -1 0 0/move Leah 0 -8 0 true/move farmer 0 -8 0 true/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 1000/speak Leah \"Let's find a more secluded spot this time...$l / 这次找个更僻静的地方吧……$l\"/playMusic none/pause 2000/end dialogue Leah \"Well, the picnic didn't pan out like I wanted it to.$h\"",
        "181928/f Penny 2000/t 900 1600/w sunny/G !IS_PASSIVE_FESTIVAL_TODAY TroutDerby, !SEASON_DAY summer 17 summer 18 summer 19": "50s/-1000 -1000/farmer 75 40 2 Penny 71 45 2 Jas 71 49 3 Vincent 70 49 1/skippable/specificTemporarySprite pennyFieldTrip/positionOffset Penny 0 -16/animate Jas false true 90 16 17 18 19/viewport 71 45 true/move farmer 0 5 3/pause 600/faceDirection Penny 1/pause 600/speak Penny \"Oh, @! It's perfect timing that you showed up. / @！你来得正好。\"/emote farmer 8/speak Penny \"I brought the children on a little field trip into the countryside. / 我要带孩子们去郊外农场进行一次小小的郊游。#$b#You know all about life in the country, right?$h / 你对乡下生活很了解吧？$h\"/speak Penny \"$q -1 null#So I was thinking... could you be my guest speaker today? / 所以我就想……今天你能当我们的客座解说员吗？#$r -1 10 event_speaker_yes#I'd love to! / 我很乐意。#$r -1 0 event_speaker_yes#Sure. / 当然。#$r -1 -1500 event_speaker_no#No... I can't stand kids. / 不……我受不了小孩。\"/fork eventEnd/faceDirection Penny 2/faceDirection farmer 2/showFrame Penny 26/pause 500/shake Penny 500/speak Penny \"Jas! Vincent! May I have your attention please! / 贾斯！文森特！听我说！\"/pause 80/stopAnimation Jas/faceDirection Jas 0 true/faceDirection Vincent 0/jump Vincent/jump Jas/pause 800/speed Vincent 4/speed Jas 4/move Vincent 0 -3 0 true/move Jas 0 -3 0 true/showFrame Penny 0/faceDirection Penny 2/faceDirection farmer 3/speak Penny \"I have a very special guest here to talk to you today... our very own local farmer, @. / 我要为你们介绍一位特殊的嘉宾……我们当地的农夫，@。#$b#He has first-hand experience living in the countryside... so he knows all about the valley's 'natural resources'! / 他对农村生活有着切身的体会……他知道谷里所有的“自然资源”！^She has first-hand experience living in the countryside... so she knows all about the valley's 'natural resources'! / 她对农村生活有着切身的体会……她知道谷里所有的“自然资源”！\"/pause 500/speak Penny \"Can anyone tell me what a 'natural resource' is? / 有人能告诉我什么是“自然资源”吗？\"/animate Jas false true 50 20 21/animate Vincent false true 50 16 17/playSound dwop/pause 1200/speak Penny \"Jas? / 贾斯？\"/stopAnimation Vincent/stopAnimation Jas/speak Jas \"A natural resource is a material source of wealth that occurs in a natural state and has economic value.$4 / 自然资源就是在自然状态下演化形成的物质资源储藏，有经济价值。$4\"/faceDirection Vincent 1/speak Penny \"Very good! That's worth two star points, Jas. / 很好！这个回答可以给两颗星，贾斯。\"/speak Jas \"Yesss!$h / 好耶！$h\"/faceDirection Vincent 0/speak Penny \"Okay, now let's give @ our full attention. / 那么，我们有请 @讲话。\"/move Penny -1 0 1/move farmer -4 0 2/question fork0 \"#Country life is all about farming.#Country life is all about gathering from the wild. / #乡村生活的全部就是耕种。#乡村生活的全部就是从大自然获得馈赠。\"/fork choseFarming/pause 500/question fork0 \"#This valley is chock-full of precious minerals.#The water around here is teeming with fresh seafood.#You'll find no better lumber south of Grampleton. / #这座山谷充满了珍贵的矿物。#这里的水域里生长着许许多多新鲜的海鲜。#你在格兰普立顿南部找不出比这里更好的木材。\"/fork choseMinerals/animate Vincent false true 50 16 17/playSound dwop/pause 300/faceDirection Penny 2/pause 500/stopAnimation Vincent/speak Penny \"Yes, Vincent? / 文森特？\"/speak Vincent \"Mr. @, are you going to marry Miss Penny?$s / @先生，你会娶潘妮老师吗？$s^Ms. @... Um, do you have a boyfriend? / @女士……呃，你有男朋友吗？\"/speak Penny \"Vincent! That's not an appropriate question! Behave yourself, or I'll have to take away all your star points for the day.$a / 文森特！这问题太无礼了！注意你自己的言行，不然我就收回你今天所有的星星。$a\"/emote Vincent 28/switchEvent fieldTripEnd",
        "choseFarming": "pause 500/question fork0 \"#The valley's soil is ideal for growing delicious vegetables.#The valley's air and grass are perfect for raising animals. / #山谷的土壤非常适合种植蔬菜。#山谷的空气和青草很适合放牧。\"/fork choseAnimals/animate Vincent false true 50 16 17/playSound dwop/pause 300/faceDirection Penny 2/pause 500/stopAnimation Vincent/speak Penny \"Yes, Vincent? / 文森特？\"/speak Vincent \"Um, Farmer @? If I eat your veggies will I grow up strong like my big brother Sam? / 呃，@？如果我吃了你的蔬菜，我会长得像我哥哥山姆一样壮吗？#$b#He's so strong, I saw him lift Miss Penny clear off the ground last night when they were climbing into a tree.$h / 他好好壮啊，昨晚他和潘妮老师爬树的时候，把她整个举起来了呢。$h\"/showFrame Penny 27/jump Penny/pause 800/showFrame Penny 0/faceDirection farmer 3 true/emote Penny 12/speak Penny \"Vincent! It's not good to gossip!$a / 文森特！别乱讲！$a\"/switchEvent fieldTripEnd",
        "3910975/f Shane 1500/e 3910674/t 900 2000/w rainy": "echos/-2000 -2000/farmer 83 92 2 Shane -3000 -3000 2 Harvey -3000 -3000 2/skippable/specificTemporarySprite shaneCliffs/viewport 83 99 clamp true/pause 1000/move farmer 0 5 2/pause 500/speak Shane \"...$7 / ……$7#$b#@...$7 / @……$7\"/pause 1000/showFrame farmer 4/pause 1000/speak Shane \"I... I'm sorry...*hic*$7 / 对……对不起……*打嗝*$7#$b#...$7 / ……$7#$b#M... My life...$7 / 我……我的人生……$7#$b#It's a pathetic joke...$7 / 是个可悲的笑话……$7#$b#Look at me...$7 / 看着我……$7#$b#...$7 / ……$7#$b#Why do I even try? ...*sob*$7 / 我为什么要挣扎呢？……*抽咽*$7#$b#I'm too small and stupid to... to take control of my life...$7 / 我根本掌控不了自己的人生……$7#$b#I'm just a p... piece of soiled garbage flittering in the wind... *bluurp*$7 / 我只是……风中摇曳的一片垃圾……*打嗝*$7#$b#.........$7 / ……$7#$b#I've been coming here often lately... looking down... $7 / 我最近经常来这里……往下看……$7#$b#Here's a chance to finally take control of my life... These cliffs...$7 / 这是控制我人生的最后一个机会……这些悬崖……$7#$b#...$7 / ……$7#$b#B... bu... *blaap*... but I'm too scared, too anxious. Just like always... $7 / 但……但……*打嗝*……但是我太害怕，太焦虑。就像平时一样……$7\"/pause 1000/showFrame farmer 0/pause 2000/speak Shane \"@... All I do is work, sleep, and drink ...t... to dull the feelings of self-hatred.$7 / @……我的人生就是工作，睡觉，吃喝……到……到自我仇恨的沮丧心情。$7#$b#Why should I even go on? Tell me... T... Tell me why I shouldn't roll off this cliff right now...$7 / 为什么我还要继续？告诉我……告……告诉我为什么我不应该现在马上从悬崖边上滚下去……$7\"/pause 1000/showFrame farmer 0/pause 1000/question shaneCliffs \"#Because there's so much to live for!#Jas needs you. You're like a father to her.#It would be a sin.#The decision is your own. Just know that I'm here for you. / #因为有太多的留恋！#贾斯需要你。你就像她的父亲。#因为这会是一种罪恶。#这是你自己的决定。我只知道为了你我会一直在这里。\"/pause 500/pause 500/pause 500/pause 1000/speak Shane \"@...$7 / @……$7\"/pause 500/showFrame farmer 4/pause 1000/speak Shane \"...I think you should take me to the hospital now.$7 / ……我想你应该带我去医院了。$7\"/pause 500/showFrame farmer 0/jump farmer/pause 1500/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/playMusic none/changeLocation Hospital/warp farmer 16 7/playMusic Hospital_Ambient/warp Harvey 16 6/faceDirection farmer 0/specificTemporarySprite shaneHospital/viewport 16 6 true/pause 2000/speak Harvey \"...I've pumped his stomach and re-hydrated his body. He's going to be okay. / ……我已经帮他清洗过胃部并且对他身体进行了再水化。他会好起来的。#$b#It's good that you brought him in, though. / 总之，庆幸你及时把他送到医院。\"/faceDirection Harvey 1/emote Harvey 28/speak Harvey \"Too much alcohol is terrible for the body... but right now I'm most worried about his mental health...$s / 酒精太多会对身体造成很大负担……但是现在我最担心的是他的心理健康……$s#$b#When he comes to, I'll have a chat with him about his treatment options. I know an excellent counselor in Zuzu City... / 当他醒来时，我会和他聊聊关于他的治疗方案。我认识祖祖城的一个优秀心理学家……\"/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 1/pause 1000/speak Harvey \"Life can be painful, sometimes... / 有时，生活会很痛苦……#$b#But there's always hope for a better future. You've got to believe in that. / 但是未来总是充满美好和希望的。你得学会相信它。\"/pause 2000/end invisible Shane",
        "choseAnimals": "pause 500/animate Vincent false true 50 16 17/playSound dwop/pause 300/faceDirection Penny 2/pause 500/stopAnimation Vincent/speak Penny \"Yes, Vincent? / 文森特？\"/speak Vincent \"Farmer @? Can I put a saddle on one of your cows and ride it into town? I wanna be a real cowboy! / @？我能在您的奶牛身上套一个鞍然后骑着它到镇里吗？我想成为真正的牛仔！\"/speak Penny \"Vincent! Behave yourself. ${Mr.^Ms.}$ @ makes ${his^her}$ living working on the farm! It's not a playground.$h / 文森特！注意自己的言行！@${先生^小姐}$要靠农场为生呢！这可不是玩的地方。$h\"/switchEvent fieldTripEnd"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Events/HaleyHouse",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "150938/n emilyStones": "SunRoom/-1000 -1000/farmer -100 -100 0 Emily 15 18 2 Haley 12 18 2 Abigail 14 20 2 Caroline 13 20 2 Marnie 16 20 2/skippable/positionOffset Haley 0 32/showFrame Emily 54/showFrame Marnie 35/showFrame Haley 34/hideShadow Haley true/showFrame Abigail 53/showFrame Caroline 24/addObject 14 21 66 1/addObject 16 21 70/addObject 12 19 68 1/addObject 15 19 64 1/addObject 13 21 60 1/viewport 14 19 true/pause 4000/speak Emily \"Great... everyone has their stone. / 好的……大家都拿到石头了。#$b#Now, close your eyes, and take slow, deep breaths. Focus on your lungs. / 来，闭上双眼，然后慢慢地深呼吸。集中注意力到你的胸腔。\"/pause 3000/speak Emily \"Visualize the pure energy flowing into your body with every breath. / 想像有纯净的能量随着呼吸流进身体中。#$b#And when you exhale, feel all the tension and negative energy flowing out, leaving you more and more relaxed with every breath. / 呼气的时候，感受到压力和负能量流动出去，每次呼吸都变得更加轻松。\"/pause 3000/speak Emily \"Now, open your heart to the vibrational frequency of your stone. Do you feel anything? / 然后，用心去呼应石头的振动频率。感受到什么了？\"/pause 1000/textAboveHead Abigail \"Nope. / 没有。\"/pause 2000/textAboveHead Marnie \"I do! / 我有！\"/pause 2000/textAboveHead Caroline \"Relaxed / 很轻松\"/pause 4000/emote Haley 24/pause 1000/emote Haley 24 true/viewport move 1 -1 7000/pause 4000/fade/viewport -1000 -1000/message \"Looks like the gemstones were put to good use... / 看来宝石有很不错的效果……\"/end",
        "471942/f Emily 500/p Emily": "none/-1000 -1000/farmer -100 -100 0 Emily 20 4 3/skippable/showFrame Emily 33/specificTemporarySprite EmilySleeping/viewport 19 4 true/emote Emily 24/pause 3000/emote Emily 24/pause 3000/viewport move 0 -1 5000/pause 1000/globalFade .004/viewport -1000 -1000/playMusic EmilyDream/changeToTemporaryMap EmilyDreamscape false/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 1000/warp Emily 21 11/warp farmer 22 15/animate Emily false true 500 24 25/globalFadeToClear .005 true/viewport move 0 -1 7000/viewport 21 18/pause 8000/textAboveHead Emily \"Mui-wah / 阿弥-陀佛\"/pause 4000/textAboveHead Emily \"Muuui-wah / 阿弥弥弥-陀佛\"/pause 5000/playSound yoba/move farmer -2 0 0/pause 600/stopAnimation Emily/showFrame Emily 26/jump Emily/shake Emily 1000/pause 1000/showFrame Emily 0/pause 500/move Emily -1 0 2/move Emily 0 1 2/pause 1000/emote Emily 8/pause 500/speak Emily \"Why are you here?$u / 您怎么会在这里？$u\"/pause 1000/move Emily 0 2 2/viewport move 0 1 1500/move Emily -1 0 2/move Emily 0 1 1/faceDirection farmer 3/pause 1000/specificTemporarySprite EmilySign/faceDirection Emily 0/pause 2000/faceDirection Emily 2/pause 8000/faceDirection Emily 1/pause 1000/speak Emily \"...$u / ……$u#$b#That reminded me of something.$u / 这让我想到了一件事。$u#$b#Even the tiniest, blandest, simplest light holds a wonderful secret. / 即使最细微、柔和、单纯的光线中也会藏有一个奇妙的秘密。\"/pause 1000/speak Emily \"Nowwwwww I know why you're here. It's a sign. Hahaha!$h / 现在我知道你为什么在这里了。这是一个迹象。哈哈哈！$h\"/pause 1000/emote farmer 8/startJittering/pause 1000/playSound coin/stopJittering/warp farmer -1000 -1000/pause 500/faceDirection Emily 2/pause 50/faceDirection Emily 3/pause 200/faceDirection Emily 0/pause 500/faceDirection Emily 1/pause 1000/faceDirection Emily 2/viewport move -1 -1 5000/pause 2000/globalFade .005/viewport -2000 -2000/pause 3000/changeLocation HaleyHouse/warp Emily 20 4/globalFadeToClear .005 true/viewport 20 3/pause 3000/move Emily -2 0 2/move Emily 0 3 2/pause 2000/speak Emily \"@... There's something special about @...$u / @……有些特别的@……$u#$b#Our destinies will intersect...$u / 我们的命运将交织在一起……$u\"/pause 1500/end",
        "choseToExplain": "pause 100/textAboveHead Haley \"I doubt it... / 我深表怀疑……\"/pause 500/resetVariable/question fork2 \"#I thought we were just friends! I didn't know it was so serious!#Pierre pressured me! He wanted to sell more bouquets!#Ladies, this is completely normal! It's just a lifestyle choice... / #我认为我们只是朋友！我不知道事情这么严重！#皮埃尔向我施压！他想卖出更多花束！#女士们，这再正常不过了！这只是生活方式的选择……\"/pause 100/fork lifestyleChoice/textAboveHead Haley \"Liar! / 骗子！\"/textAboveHead Maru \"Yeah, right! / 对，没错！\"/speak Emily \"Do you really expect us to believe that? You're just digging yourself into a deeper hole...$a / 你真以为我们会相信吗？你给自己挖了一个更大的坑……$a\"/pause 1000/faceDirection Haley 2/playMusic none/speak Haley \"...I think we've come to a decision... isn't that right, girls?$u / ……我想我们已经决定了……对吗，女孩们？$u\"/pause 500/speak Penny \"...yes.$s / ……是的。$s\"/speak Leah \"Absolutely.$a / 当然。$a\"/faceDirection Haley 3/pause 1000/jump Haley/jump Abigail/jump Emily/jump Leah/jump Maru/jump Penny/pause 1000/jump Haley/jump Abigail/jump Emily/jump Leah/jump Maru/jump Penny/pause 1000/jump Haley/jump Abigail/jump Emily/jump Leah/jump Maru/jump Penny/pause 1000/speak Maru \"We're all gonna give you the cold shoulder!$a / 我们都要疏远你！$a\"/faceDirection farmer 2 true/animate farmer false true 100 94/jump farmer/playSound slimedead/pause 2000/fade/viewport -2000 -2000/dump girls 4/end warpOut",
        "haleyWontDoIt": "move Haley -2 0 0/move Haley 0 -2 0/emote Haley 12/faceDirection Emily 1/emote Emily 28/speak Emily \"*sigh*... I guess I'll just do it, then...$s / *唉*……那我去打扫吧……$s\"/pause 1000/end",
        "195012/f Haley 2500/f Emily 2500/f Penny 2500/f Abigail 2500/f Leah 2500/f Maru 2500/o Abigail/o Penny/o Leah/o Emily/o Maru/o Haley/o Shane/o Harvey/o Sebastian/o Sam/o Elliott/o Alex/e 38/e 2123343/e 10/e 901756/e 54/e 15/k 195019": "playful/-1000 -1000/farmer 8 19 1 Haley 18 18 1 Emily 19 17 2 Penny 20 17 2 Maru 21 17 2 Leah 22 18 3 Abigail 20 20 0 Pierre -1000 -1000 1/move farmer 5 0 1 true/viewport 17 19 true/move false/pause 500/startJittering/faceDirection farmer 2 true/animate farmer false true 100 94/jump farmer/pause 2000/stopAnimation farmer/showFrame farmer 0/stopJittering/playSound thudStep/faceDirection farmer 3 true/showFrame farmer 7 true/startJittering/faceDirection Haley 3 true/faceDirection Emily 3 true/faceDirection Penny 3 true/faceDirection Maru 3 true/faceDirection Leah 3 true/faceDirection Abigail 3 true/textAboveHead Haley \"Not so fast! / 别跑那么快！\"/textAboveHead Abigail \"Hold it! / 别动！\"/textAboveHead Leah \"Stop! / 站住！\"/pause 3000/stopJittering/showFrame farmer 6 true/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 1/move farmer 3 0 1/playMusic none/emote farmer 28/pause 500/speak Abigail \"Never thought you'd find all your 'girlfriends' in one room, huh @?$a / 呵，没想到你所有的“女朋友”会出现在一个房间里吧，@？$a\"/pause 500/speak Leah \"I... I thought you were different than other men...$s / 我……我还以为你和其他男人不一样……$s^You tricked all of us into thinking we loved you... You're horrible...$a / 你骗取了我们所有人的爱……你真是太可怕了……$a\"/pause 500/speak Penny \"How could you do this to us, @?$s / 你怎么能这样对我们，@？$s\"/pause 500/speak Maru \"You think you're real smooth, don't you? Thought you'd sample the whole 'buffet', huh? What a sleeze...$a / 你真觉得自己是情场高手，是吗？以为自己游刃有余、如鱼得水？真是个花心大萝卜……$a\"/pause 500/speak Emily \"Th... That night in the tent... you whispered such sweet things to me in the dark...$s / 那……那天晚上在帐篷里……黑暗中你在我耳边轻声说了那么多甜言蜜语……$s#$b#Now I have to face each day knowing it was all a lie.$s / 原来一切都是谎言，现在知道真相的我，该如何面对每一天……$s\"/pause 500/playMusic ragtime/speak Haley \"Well, us women stick together! And we're not going to put up with this!$a / 好了，我们女人要团结起来！我们不能忍受这种事情！$a^Well, we're not going to put up with your abuse any longer!$a / 我们不会再忍受你的伤害了！$a\"/textAboveHead Leah \"That's right! / 没错！\"/pause 500/speak Abigail \"Well? What do you have to say for yourself?$a / 嗯？你还有什么要为自己辩解的？$a\"/pause 1000/question fork1 \"#I'm sorry... what I did was wrong.#Ladies, calm down! I can explain... / #对不起……我以前做错了。#女士们，冷静一下！我可以解释……\"/fork choseToExplain/pause 500/textAboveHead Maru \"Hmmph... / 哼……\"/pause 500/speak Abigail \"Nice try, but that's not going to cut it...$u / 说得好听，但这事不能就这么算了……$u\"/pause 1000/playMusic none/speak Haley \"...so we've come to a decision... isn't that right, girls?$u / ……我们已经决定了……对吗，女孩们？$u\"/pause 500/speak Penny \"...yes.$s / ……是的。$s\"/speak Leah \"Absolutely.$a / 当然。$a\"/pause 1000/jump Haley/jump Abigail/jump Emily/jump Leah/jump Maru/jump Penny/pause 1000/speak Maru \"We're all gonna give you the cold shoulder!$a / 我们都要疏远你！$a\"/faceDirection farmer 2 true/animate farmer false true 100 94/jump farmer/playSound slimedead/pause 2000/fade/viewport -2000 -2000/dump girls 3/end warpOut",
        "15/f Haley 2500/p Haley": "Hospital_Ambient/-1000 -1000/farmer 5 9 0 Haley -100 -100 2/skippable/specificTemporarySprite haleyRoomDark/viewport 5 4 true/pause 500/emote farmer 8/move farmer 0 -4 0/move farmer -1 0 0/move farmer 0 -1 0/pause 1000/animate farmer false false 650 15/playSound woodyStep/pause 200/playSound woodyStep/pause 200/playSound woodyStep/pause 200/pause 800/speak Haley \"Come in! Just make sure to close the door quickly behind you! / 进来吧！记得快点把门关上！\"/pause 1000/warp farmer -100 -100/playSound doorClose/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/changeToTemporaryMap Darkroom false/warp Haley 1 5/warp farmer 3 7/viewport 4 4 true/pause 800/faceDirection Haley 2/jump Haley/pause 600/speak Haley \"@, you're here! / @你来啦！\"/move farmer 0 -1 3/move farmer -1 0 0/move farmer 0 -1 3/faceDirection Haley 1/speak Haley \"Welcome to my brand new dark room!$h / 欢迎来到我的新暗室。$h\"/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 1/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 0/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 3/pause 500/speak Haley \"$q -1 null#So... what do you think? / 你觉得怎么样？#$r -1 10 Event_darkroom1#It looks great! / 看起来非常棒！#$r -1 0 Event_darkroom2#What does it do? / 这是干什么的？#$r -1 -50 Event_darkroom3#I've seen better. / 我见过比这更好的。\"/faceDirection Haley 0/emote Haley 40/pause 500/speak Haley \"Um... so, anyway... what do you want to do?$s / 唔……话说回来……有什么事吗？$s\"/faceDirection Haley 0/question haleyDarkRoom \" #Offer to help decorate the dark room.#Make an excuse and leave.#Try to kiss her. / #提出帮忙装修暗室。#找个借口离开。#亲吻她。\"/faceDirection Haley 1/fork leave/playMusic musicboxsong/pause 500/pause 1000/emote Haley 16/pause 400/positionOffset farmer 16 0 true/animate farmer true true 100 101/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 50/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 50/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 50/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 50/showFrame Haley 28/pause 500/positionOffset Haley 2 0/pause 50/positionOffset farmer -2 0/positionOffset Haley 2 0/pause 50/positionOffset farmer -2 0/positionOffset Haley 2 0/pause 50/positionOffset farmer -2 0/positionOffset Haley 2 0/pause 50/positionOffset farmer -2 0/positionOffset Haley 2 0/pause 50/positionOffset farmer -2 0/positionOffset Haley 2 0/pause 50/positionOffset farmer -2 0/positionOffset Haley 2 0/pause 50/positionOffset farmer -2 0/positionOffset Haley 2 0/pause 50/pause 700/playSound dwop/specificTemporarySprite heart 2 4/pause 3000/speak Haley \"Oh, @... I've been waiting so long for you to do that.$11 / 哦……@……我早就想这么做了。$11\"/pause 2000/speak Haley \"One moment...$l / 等一下……$l\"/pause 400/showFrame Haley 4/stopAnimation farmer/faceDirection farmer 3/pause 600/showFrame Haley 29/pause 300/playSound openBox/ambientLight 255 180 180/pause 500/faceDirection Haley 1/pause 1000/showFrame Haley 28/positionOffset farmer 16 0 true/animate farmer true true 100 101/positionOffset Haley 2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Haley 2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Haley 2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Haley 2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Haley 2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Haley 2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Haley 2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Haley 2 0/pause 50/pause 4000/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 1000/end dialogue Haley \"That was nice...$l\"",
        "12/f Haley 1000/p Haley": "ragtime/-1000 -1000/farmer 16 20 1 Haley 18 16 0/skippable/showFrame Haley 20/shake Haley 500/viewport 15 16 true/pause 500/shake Haley 500/pause 500/speak Haley \"Nnnnnghhh... I just can't get this jar open!$a / 唔嗯嗯嗯……我打不开这个罐子！$a#$b#...$s / ……$s\"/pause 400/shake Haley 500/move farmer 0 -4 1/shake Haley 500/move farmer 1 0 1/pause 500/faceDirection Haley 3 true/showFrame Haley 21/emote Haley 16/speak Haley \"Oh! It's you...@, right? / 噢！是你啊……@对吧？\"/pause 1000/speak Haley \"$q 47 null#Say... you're pretty strong, aren't you? / 话说……你挺有劲的，对吧？#$r 47 30 Event_jar1#Yes / 是#$r 47 -30 Event_jar2#No / 不是\"/faceDirection Haley 3/animate farmer false true 100 111/pause 400/playSound fishingRodBend/startJittering/pause 500/stopJittering/pause 200/playSound fishingRodBend/startJittering/pause 500/stopJittering/pause 200/playSound fishingRodBend/startJittering/pause 2000/stopJittering/playSound coin/stopAnimation farmer/animate farmer false true 100 112/jump farmer/pause 1500/pause 200/stopAnimation farmer/faceDirection farmer 1/showFrame Haley 21/speak Haley \"Hey, you did it! You're stronger than you look!$h / 你还真打开了诶！你比看起来还要强壮！$h\"/pause 400/emote farmer 12/pause 500/emote Haley 20/pause 500/speak Haley \"Thanks!$h / 谢谢！$h\"/pause 500/end",
        "lifestyleChoice": "pause 100/speak Penny \"Hmmph! I don't know what's considered 'normal' in Zuzu City, but I'm definitely not okay with this arrangement!$a / 哼！我不知道在祖祖城什么是“正常”，但我绝对不会接受！$a\"/speak Maru \"It's not a 'choice' if none of us even know about it!$a / 如果我们根本不知道的话，那这就不是“选择”！$a\"/pause 100/speak Abigail \"You can't weasel your way out of this one, @.$a / 你别想这样蒙混过关，@。$a\"/pause 1000/faceDirection Haley 2/playMusic none/speak Haley \"...I think we've come to a decision... isn't that right, girls?$u / ……我想我们已经决定了……对吗，女孩们？$u\"/pause 500/speak Penny \"...yes.$s / ……是的。$s\"/speak Leah \"Absolutely.$a / 当然。$a\"/faceDirection Haley 3/pause 1000/jump Haley/jump Abigail/jump Emily/jump Leah/jump Maru/jump Penny/pause 1000/jump Haley/jump Abigail/jump Emily/jump Leah/jump Maru/jump Penny/pause 1000/jump Haley/jump Abigail/jump Emily/jump Leah/jump Maru/jump Penny/pause 1000/speak Maru \"We're all gonna give you the cold shoulder!$a / 我们都要疏远你！$a\"/faceDirection farmer 2 true/animate farmer false true 100 94/jump farmer/playSound slimedead/pause 2000/fade/viewport -2000 -2000/dump girls 4/end warpOut",
        "917409/e 463391/f Emily 1500/p Emily": "none/-1000 -1000/farmer 16 10 0 Emily 14 6 2/specificTemporarySprite EmilyBoomBox/skippable/viewport 14 6 true/move farmer 0 -2 3/move farmer -2 0 0/speak Emily \"Come in, @! I want to show you something.$h / 请进@！我要向你展示一样东西。$h\"/pause 500/move farmer 0 -1 0/pause 500/speak Emily \"It's my secret hobby... I've been practicing for months. / 这是我的一个秘密爱好……我已经练习好几个月了。#$b#Now, sit back, relax, and allow yourself to be carried away to a better place... okay? / 现在，坐好，放松，想象自己被带到一个很美好的地方……好了吗？\"/stopMusic/pause 600/move Emily 0 -1 0/faceDirection Emily 0/pause 500/playMusic EmilyDance/pause 1240/faceDirection Emily 2 true/pause 3220/specificTemporarySprite EmilyBoomBoxStart/animate Emily false true 430 0 27/pause 6500/animate Emily false true 440 31 39/pause 6470/doAction 14 4/pause 400/specificTemporarySprite EmilySongBackLights/animate Emily false true 220 18 19 18 19 18 19 18 19 18 19 18 19 18 19 18 19 20 21 20 21 20 21 20 21 20 21 20 21 20 21 20 21 16 17 16 17 16 17 16 17 16 17 16 17 16 17 16 17 22 23 22 23 22 23 22 23 22 23 22 23 22 23 22 23/glow 0 0 255 true/pause 1000/glow 0 255 255 false/pause 1760/glow 0 0 255 false/pause 1760/glow 255 0 255 false/pause 1760/glow 255 255 0 false/pause 1760/glow 0 255 255 false/pause 1760/glow 0 255 0 false/pause 1760/glow 255 0 0 false/pause 1760/glow 0 0 255 false/pause 1000/jump Emily/glow 255 0 255 false/pause 1760/glow 0 0 255 false/pause 1760/glow 255 0 255 false/pause 1760/glow 255 255 0 false/pause 1760/glow 0 255 255 false/pause 1760/glow 0 255 0 false/pause 1760/glow 255 0 0 false/pause 1760/glow 0 0 255 false/pause 1260/animate Emily false true 440 31 39/pause 1760/glow 255 255 0/pause 1760/glow 255 0 255/pause 1760/glow 0 255 255/pause 1760/glow 255 0 0/pause 1760/glow 0 0 255/pause 1760/glow 0 255 0/pause 1760/glow 255 0 255/pause 1760/glow 255 0 255 false/stopAnimation Emily/specificTemporarySprite EmilyBoomBoxStop/faceDirection Emily 2/emote farmer 16/pause 1000/animate Emily false true 300 50 51/pause 1600/speak Emily \"$q 213 null#So... *gasp*... what did you think?$h / 所以……*喘气*……你感觉怎么样？$h#$r 213 25 event_dance1#That was amazing! / 这太奇妙了！#$r 213 -50 event_dance2#That was embarrassing... / 真尴尬……#$r 213 25 event_dance1#(Say nothing and do a slow clap) / （保持沉默并缓缓鼓掌）\"/emote Emily 28/speak Emily \"Phew... that was quite a workout...$u / 唷……这东西太消耗体力了……$u\"/pause 500/stopAnimation Emily/showFrame Emily 0/pause 1000/animate Emily false true 100 48 49/pause 1000/speak Emily \"I haven't been this sweaty since I ordered the pepper platter at Abigail's graduation fiesta!$h / 自从我在阿比盖尔的毕业典礼上点了一盘胡椒食物后，我再也没有出过这么多汗！$h\"/pause 1000/stopAnimation Emily/speak Emily \"...Well, I'd better take a shower. Thanks for watching. / ……嗯，我最好洗个澡。感谢你来看我表演。\"/pause 500/faceDirection Emily 2/end dialogue Emily \"Don't tell anyone about the dance. That was for your eyes only.\"",
        "11/f Haley 500/p Haley/p Emily": "50s/6 20/farmer -10 -10 0 Haley 5 20 1 Emily 8 20 3/skippable/pause 1000/shake Haley 500/pause 500/speak Haley \"Urgghh! I always clean under the cushions! It's YOUR turn this week!$a / 呃啊啊！老是我打扫坐垫下面！这周轮到你了！$a\"/emote Emily 12/speak Emily \"You're being childish, Haley. I do the vast majority of work in this house, and you know it.$u / 你真孩子气，海莉。这房子里大部分的家务都是我做的，你心知肚明。$u\"/pause 200/warp farmer 2 24/playSound doorClose/pause 400/faceDirection Haley 2/faceDirection Emily 2/speak Haley \"Oh, it's that new ${farm boy^girl from the farm}$.$7 / 哦，是那个新来的农场${男孩^女孩}$。$7\"/faceDirection Emily 3/speak Emily \"${He^She}$ has a name, you know.$u / ${他^她}$有名字的。$u\"/move farmer 0 -1 1/move farmer 3 0 0/faceDirection Emily 2/speak Haley \"Hey, I bet you'll understand my point of view here. / 嘿，你会理解我的。\"/emote farmer 8/speak Emily \"*sigh*... I'm really sorry to involve you in this, @. Haley is complaining because I asked her to clean under the cushions.$u / *唉*……抱歉把你牵扯进来了，@。海莉在抱怨我让她打扫坐垫下面。$u\"/faceDirection Haley 1/speak Haley \"$q 45 null#It's only because I cleaned them last week!$a / 那是因为上周是我打扫的！$a#$r 46 -50 Event_clean2#Stop whining and just clean it! / 少废话，赶紧打扫！#$r 45 30 Event_clean1#Haley, why not have this be your one weekly job? / 海莉，何不每周固定打扫一次呢？#$r 46 -30 Event_clean3#Emily, take the high road and do it this time. / 艾米丽，这次就去打扫吧。\"/fork haleyWontDoIt/stopMusic/faceDirection Haley 3/emote Haley 12/pause 400/faceDirection Haley 1/speak Haley \"Alright, you win. I guess this can be my job every week. Then there won't be any reason to argue over it.$u / 好吧，你赢了。不出意外这就成了我每周的工作了。然后就不用再争吵了。$u\"/faceDirection Haley 2/speak Emily \"Thanks, @. That was a great solution.$h / 非常感谢。@。圆满解决了呢。$h\"/pause 1000/end",
        "195019/f Haley 2500/f Emily 2500/f Penny 2500/f Abigail 2500/f Leah 2500/f Maru 2500/o Abigail/o Penny/o Leah/o Emily/o Maru/o Haley/o Shane/o Harvey/o Sebastian/o Sam/o Elliott/o Alex/e 38/e 2123343/e 10/e 901756/e 54/e 15/i 446/k 195012": "playful/-1000 -1000/farmer 8 19 1 Haley 18 18 1 Emily 19 17 2 Penny 20 17 2 Maru 21 17 2 Leah 22 18 3 Abigail 20 20 0/pause 1000/message \"For some reason, you decide to place your hand in your pocket... / 出于某些原因，你决定把手放到口袋里……\"/pause 500/message \"You touch the rabbit's foot, and feel a sense of relief... / 你摸着兔子的脚，感觉如释重负……\"/move farmer 5 0 1 true/viewport 17 19 true/move false/pause 500/faceDirection Haley 3 true/faceDirection Emily 3 true/faceDirection Penny 3 true/faceDirection Maru 3 true/faceDirection Leah 3 true/faceDirection Abigail 3 true/textAboveHead Haley \"Hi! / 嗨！\"/textAboveHead Abigail \"Hey there! / 嘿！\"/textAboveHead Leah \"Look who it is! / 看谁来了！\"/pause 2000/move farmer 4 0 1/emote farmer 32/pause 500/speak Abigail \"We were just gossiping about Mayor Lewis and Marnie...$h / 我们刚才在聊刘易斯镇长和玛妮的八卦……$h\"/pause 500/speak Penny \"Personally, I don't think there's anything fishy going on between them... / 我个人觉得他们之间没有什么猫腻……\"/pause 500/speak Haley \"Hah! Were you born yesterday?$h / 哈！你太天真了吧？$h\"/jump Penny/emote Penny 12/fade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 1500/message \"You spent a short while with the group. / 你和女生小团体待了一会儿。\"/pause 1000/message \"It was an uneventful gathering! / 这次聚会无事发生！\"/pause 500/end"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Events/HarveyRoom",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "normal": "pause 400/speak Harvey \"Sorry I'm all disheveled... I didn't know you were coming over.$h / 抱歉，我邋邋遢遢的……我不知道你要过来。$h\"/move farmer 0 -2 0/pause 600/speak Harvey \"Hey, I think I hear a plane overhead... / 嘿，我好像听见头上有飞机声……\"/move Harvey 0 1 3/move Harvey -3 0 0/move Harvey 0 -2 0/speak Harvey \"@, get over here! / @，快过来！\"/move farmer 0 -1 3/move farmer -4 0 0/move farmer 0 -2 0/speak Harvey \"Look! / 快看！\"/globalFade/cutscene plane/viewport -1000 -1000/speak Harvey \"As a kid, my dream was always to be a pilot. / 小时候，我的梦想就是当飞行员。\"/pause 1000/speak Harvey \"...But with my bad eyesight and a crippling fear of heights, that dream started to fade away.$s / 但因为我视力不好，而且极度恐高，这个梦想已经渐渐暗淡了。$s\"/faceDirection Harvey 3/faceDirection farmer 1/viewport 5 6 true/pause 1000/emote farmer 28/speak Harvey \"It's okay... don't be sad. / 没事的……不用伤心。#$b#I've grown to accept my station in life. Not everyone can achieve their dreams... that's just the way the world is. / 我长大了，能接受自己人生的定位了。不是所有人都能实现梦想的……世界就是这样的。\"/pause 1600/speak Harvey \"Hey, let me show you my model airplanes. I just finished the new TR-Starbird deluxe set.$h / 嘿，你来看看我的飞机模型。我刚刚完成新的 TR-星鸟豪华版。$h\"/advancedMove Harvey false 0 2 4 0/faceDirection farmer 2/end"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Events/Hospital",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "7/f Maru 1000/p Maru": "Hospital_Ambient/-1000 -1000/farmer -10000 -10000 0 Maru 9 15 3 Harvey 7 10 0/skippable/changeSprite Maru Hospital/changePortrait Maru Hospital/showFrame Maru 18/viewport 10 15/pause 4000/speak Maru \"*sigh*... I'm so sick of preparing these samples...$s / *叹息*……我对于准备这些样本很不在行……$s\"/pause 2000/playSound doorClose/warp farmer 10 19/pause 100/playSound throw/showFrame Maru 17/shake Maru 2000/jump Maru/specificTemporarySprite maruBeaker/move farmer 0 -1 0/pause 1250/showFrame Maru 0/faceDirection Maru 2/pause 100/speak Maru \"Agh! Oh no!... $4 / 啊！糟糕！$4\"/pause 600/showFrame Maru 16/pause 1000/speak Maru \"The whole sample is ruined... Harvey's going to kill me...$s / 整份样本都被毁了……哈维会把我杀了……$s\"/pause 600/showFrame Maru 0/faceDirection Maru 0/pause 1500/faceDirection Maru 2/pause 400/speak Maru \"$q 38 null#@, what should I do? / @，我应该怎么办？#$r 38 -50 Event_Hospital_1#Just scoop it off the floor. He won't know the difference. / 从地板上铲起来就好。他不会发现的。#$r 39 -20 Event_Hospital_2#Tell Harvey it was my fault. / 告诉哈维是我的错。#$r 38 50 Event_Hospital_3#Tell Harvey it was an accident. / 告诉哈维，这纯属意外。\"/move Harvey 3 0 2/move Harvey 0 2 2/doAction 10 13/move Harvey 0 1 2/faceDirection Maru 1/speak Harvey \"What happened? I heard something break. / 发生了什么？我听到东西打碎的声音。\"/pause 500/speak Maru \"$p 38#I accidentally dropped one of the samples... I'm so sorry.$s / 我不小心摔碎了一份样本……真是对不起。$s|@ came in and slammed the door so loud I dropped this sample.$u / @进来后猛地一关门，吓得我打碎了一份样本。$u\"/fork toldTruth/move Harvey 0 2 3/emote Harvey 40/speak Harvey \"You shouldn't blame others for your own problems, Maru.$a / 玛鲁，你不能把自己的问题推卸到别人身上。$a\"/pause 300/faceDirection Harvey 1/speak Harvey \"*sigh*... I'll have to call the patient back in to recollect this sample.$s / *唉*……我只好让病人再来采集一次样本了。$s#$b#This'll probably put us in the red for another month...$s / 这很可能会害得我们又亏损一个月……$s\"/pause 600/faceDirection Maru 2/pause 1000/showFrame Maru 16/pause 500/emote farmer 28/end",
        "571102/f Harvey 2000": "Hospital_Ambient/-100 -100/farmer -200 -2000 0 Harvey 4 5 0/skippable/changeLocation HarveyRoom/showFrame Harvey 23/viewport 5 6 true/pause 1000/speak Harvey \"Hello? Hello? Is anyone out there?$9 / 喂？喂？有谁在吗？$9\"/pause 1300/emote Harvey 40/speak Harvey \"This is Dr. H at... 52 North 43.5 East... Seeking aerial response...Anyone out there?$9 / 我是 H 医生……这里是北纬 52 度东经 43.5 度……正在进行无线电呼叫……有人听到吗？$9\"/pause 2000/emote Harvey 40/pause 700/playSound newArtifact/message \"Copy.. Dr. H on the ground... this is Blackbird Fiver Fiver Zuzu. Anything to report? / 收到……地面的 H 医生……这里是黑鸟 55Z。有事汇报吗？\"/showFrame Harvey 28/jump Harvey/pause 800/speak Harvey \"Someone's there!?$10 / 真有人听到了吗！？$10#$b#Er... I mean!... Standard ground report: Wind at 3 Clicks, 36 Degrees North of West. Ground Temperature at 42 Kraggs. Humidity 53%. Dr. H out!$10 / 地面情报汇报：风速 3KPH，风向西偏北 36 度。地面温度 42 度。湿度 53%。H 医生通话结束！$10\"/pause 300/playMusic kindadumbautumn/faceDirection Harvey 1 true/move Harvey 2 0 1/speak Harvey \"Yikes, my pulse is soaring...$7 / 啊，我的脉搏在上升……$7\"/pause 400/playSound doorClose/warp farmer 6 12/move farmer 0 -3 0/faceDirection Harvey 2/speak Harvey \"@! / @！\"/question fork1 \"#Ask Harvey why he's all flustered.#Pretend like everything's normal. / #询问哈维他为何那么紧张。#假装一切正常。\"/fork normal/pause 500/speak Harvey \"Ah, well... You see, I was just on my radio here... and I made contact with a real pilot! / 啊，我正在进行无线电通讯……而我居然遇到了真正的飞行员！\"/emote Harvey 16/speak Harvey \"As a matter of fact, we can probably see him flying overhead right now! / 现在应该就能看到他从我们头顶飞过！\"/move Harvey 0 1 3/move Harvey -3 0 0/move Harvey 0 -2 0/speak Harvey \"Quick, get over here! / 快点，快过来！\"/speed farmer 4/move farmer 0 -3 3/speed farmer 4/move farmer -4 0 0/speed farmer 4/move farmer 0 -2 0/speed farmer 4/speak Harvey \"Look! / 快看！\"/globalFade/cutscene plane/viewport -1000 -1000/speak Harvey \"As a kid, my dream was always to be a pilot. / 小时候，我的梦想就是当飞行员。\"/pause 1000/speak Harvey \"...But with my bad eyesight and a crippling fear of heights, that dream started to fade away.$s / 但因为我视力不好，而且极度恐高，这个梦想已经渐渐暗淡了。$s\"/faceDirection Harvey 3/faceDirection farmer 1/viewport 5 6 true/pause 1600/emote farmer 28/speak Harvey \"It's okay... don't be sad. / 没事的……不用替我遗憾。#$b#I've grown to accept my station in life. Not everyone can achieve their dreams... that's just the way the world is. / 我长大了，能接受自己人生的定位了。不是所有人都能实现梦想的……人生就是这样的。\"/pause 1600/speak Harvey \"Hey, let me show you my model airplanes. I just finished the new TR-Starbird deluxe set.$h / 嘿，你来看看我的飞机模型。我刚刚完成新的 TR-星鸟豪华版。$h\"/advancedMove Harvey false 0 2 16 0/faceDirection farmer 2/globalFade .003/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 500/end",
        "toldTruth": "move Harvey 0 2 3/speak Harvey \"Thanks for telling me the truth, Maru. / 玛鲁，谢谢你告诉我事实真相。#$b#Don't worry about the sample, we'll just get another one. / 不用担心样本的事情，我们会再采集一份。\"/pause 500/emote Harvey 32/pause 500/speak Maru \"Thanks for being patient with me, Doctor Harvey. / 谢谢你对我的包容，哈维医生。\"/pause 500/speak Harvey \"Of course... you've been a big help around here. I don't know what I'd do without you! / 当然……你在这儿帮了我不少忙。没有你，我都不知道该怎么办！\"/pause 500/emote Maru 32/pause 1000/faceDirection Harvey 2/pause 500/emote Harvey 8/speak Harvey \"@? You look a little pale... are you feeling okay? / @？你的脸色有些苍白……你还好吗？\"/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 2/emote farmer 28/end",
        "PlayerKilled": "none/-100 -100/farmer 20 12 2 Harvey 21 12 3/pause 1500/showFrame 5/message \" ...{0}? / ……{0}？\"/pause 1000/message \"Easy, now... take it slow. / 好了，放轻松……慢慢来。\"/viewport 20 12 true/pause 1000/speak Harvey \"Someone found you unconscious and battered... I had to perform an emergency surgery on you! / 有人发现你不省人事地倒在地上……所以我给你做了紧急手术！#$b#Be a little more careful next time, okay?$s / 下次小心点，好吗？$s\"/showFrame 0/pause 1000/emote farmer 28/hospitaldeath/end",
        "57/f Harvey 1000/p Harvey": "sweet/-100 -100/farmer 10 19 0 Harvey 9 14 3/skippable/doAction 10 13/viewport 10 14/move farmer 0 -2 0/pause 300/faceDirection Harvey 2/speak Harvey \"Ah, @! I was just about to write you a letter. / @！我正要给你写信呢。\"/faceDirection farmer 0/emote farmer 8/speak Harvey \"You see, my records indicate that you're due for your annual checkup! / 我的记录显示，你该进行一年一度的体检了！\"/emote farmer 28/speak Harvey \"Now, now... There's no need to worry. It'll be quick and painless. Please follow me. / 现在就开始吧……用不着担心。一下下就好，一点儿也不疼。请跟我来。\"/pause 600/advancedMove Harvey false 1 0 0 -4 -5 0/move farmer 0 -7 0 false/move farmer -4 0 3 true/viewport move -1 -2 4500/proceedPosition Harvey 5 10/doAction 5 9/move Harvey 0 -5 2 false/move farmer -1 0 0 false/move farmer 0 -4 0 false/pause 500/speak Harvey \"Hmm... Okay. Hold still, please. / 嗯……好。请待着别动。\"/pause 2000/speak Harvey \"Say 'ahhh...' / 说“啊啊啊……”\"/pause 500/speak Harvey \"Okay, you can stop. / 好，可以啦。\"/pause 600/move Harvey -1 0 0/pause 1000/showFrame Harvey 19/playSound openBox/pause 1000/showFrame Harvey 8/move Harvey 0 1 1/faceDirection farmer 3/speak Harvey \"I just need to check your vitals. / 我只要检查一下你的重要器官。\"/pause 800/animate Harvey false true 100 4 5 6 7/positionOffset Harvey 2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Harvey 2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Harvey 2 2/pause 50/positionOffset Harvey 2 2/pause 50/positionOffset Harvey 2 2/pause 50/positionOffset Harvey 2 2/pause 50/positionOffset Harvey 2 2/pause 50/positionOffset Harvey 2 2/pause 50/stopAnimation Harvey/showFrame Harvey 20/pause 150/showFrame Harvey 21/pause 1500/speak Harvey \"$q 86 null#Hmm... Your pulse is high.$u / 嗯……你的心跳有点儿快。$u#$r 86 20 event_heart1#I'm a little nervous... / 我有点紧张。#$r 86 20 event_heart2#I'm out of breath from working on the farm. / 我刚才在农场里干活，现在还没喘过来气。#$r 86 -50 event_heart3#Are you really a doctor? My pulse is fine! / 你真的是医生吗？我的心跳很正常！\"/pause 800/showFrame Harvey 20/pause 150/showFrame Harvey 4/animate Harvey false true 100 7 6 5 4/positionOffset Harvey -2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Harvey -2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Harvey -2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Harvey -2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Harvey -2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Harvey -2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Harvey -2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Harvey -2 0/pause 50/stopAnimation Harvey/pause 1300/speak Harvey \"Well, then! You seem very healthy, @. / 好啦！看来你身体很好，@。#$b#Just make sure not to overwork yourself on that farm! / 只要当心干活儿别太累着就好！\"/emote farmer 32/pause 800/move farmer 0 1 2 true/faceDirection Harvey 2 true/move farmer 0 1 2/speak Harvey \"Thanks for stopping in.$h / 感谢你来就诊。$h\"/faceDirection farmer 0 true/end"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Events/IslandHut",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "1039573/N 10/Hl addedParrotBoy": "continue/-1000 -1000/farmer 7 12 0/broadcastEvent/skippable/specificTemporarySprite removeSprite 777/addTemporaryActor ParrotBoy 16 32 5 2 2 true ???/pause 2000/viewport 5 7 true/move farmer 0 -4 0/pause 2000/emote ParrotBoy 8/pause 500/playMusic sad_kid/animate ParrotBoy false true 200 20 21/playSound Cowboy_Footstep/positionOffset ParrotBoy 0 16/pause 200/playSound Cowboy_Footstep/positionOffset ParrotBoy 0 16/pause 200/playSound Cowboy_Footstep/positionOffset ParrotBoy 0 16/pause 200/playSound Cowboy_Footstep/positionOffset ParrotBoy 0 16/pause 200/playSound Cowboy_Footstep/positionOffset ParrotBoy 0 16/pause 200/playSound Cowboy_Footstep/positionOffset ParrotBoy 0 16/pause 200/playSound Cowboy_Footstep/positionOffset ParrotBoy 0 16/pause 200/playSound Cowboy_Footstep/positionOffset ParrotBoy 0 16/pause 200/playSound Cowboy_Footstep/positionOffset ParrotBoy 0 16/pause 200/playSound Cowboy_Footstep/positionOffset ParrotBoy 0 16/pause 200/playSound Cowboy_Footstep/positionOffset ParrotBoy 0 16/pause 200/playSound Cowboy_Footstep/positionOffset ParrotBoy 0 16/pause 200/playSound Cowboy_Footstep/positionOffset ParrotBoy 0 16/pause 200/playSound Cowboy_Footstep/positionOffset ParrotBoy 0 16/pause 200/playSound Cowboy_Footstep/positionOffset ParrotBoy 0 16/pause 200/playSound Cowboy_Footstep/positionOffset ParrotBoy 0 16/pause 200/playSound Cowboy_Footstep/stopAnimation ParrotBoy/faceDirection ParrotBoy 2/pause 500/move ParrotBoy 0 2 2/faceDirection farmer 3 true/move ParrotBoy 1 0 1/pause 1000/speak ParrotBoy \"...$u / ……$u#$b#...Y...You... Bird friend?$u / ……你……你……鸟儿朋友？$u\"/pause 1000/animate ParrotBoy false true 500 19/pause 200/positionOffset ParrotBoy 16 0/playSound slimeHit/startJittering/pause 200/positionOffset ParrotBoy -16 0/stopJittering/pause 600/positionOffset ParrotBoy 16 0/playSound slimeHit/startJittering/pause 200/positionOffset ParrotBoy -16 0/stopJittering/pause 600/stopAnimation ParrotBoy/pause 1500/speak ParrotBoy \"...Seem good. / ……看起来不错。\"/jump ParrotBoy/pause 1500/specificTemporarySprite parrotHutSquawk/pause 10/pause 2100/animate ParrotBoy false true 500 17/playSound parrot_squawk/shake ParrotBoy 800/pause 1600/stopAnimation ParrotBoy/pause 1000/emote farmer 8/pause 500/speak ParrotBoy \"...She ask if you are bird friend. / ……她问你是不是鸟儿朋友。#$b#I told her... yes.$h / 我告诉她……是的。$h\"/pause 500/emote farmer 32/pause 300/quickQuestion #How did you end up here?#Where are your parents?(break)pause 100(break)pause 100/playMusic echos/pause 500/faceDirection ParrotBoy 2/emote ParrotBoy 28/showFrame ParrotBoy 18/pause 400/speak ParrotBoy \"...Big Storm... Waves... Lightning...$s / ……暴风雨……海浪……闪电……$s#$b#Mother... Father... swallowed by the sea...$s / 妈妈……爸爸……被大海吞没……$s#$b#I... I washed up on shore...$s / 我……海浪……带到海滩上……$s\"/pause 500/pause 500/speak ParrotBoy \"...No, no, no... Th... That was just a dream... right?$s / ……不、不、不……这……这只是个梦……对吗？$s\"/showFrame ParrotBoy 0/pause 1000/stopAnimation ParrotBoy/faceDirection ParrotBoy 1/playMusic jungle_ambience/speak ParrotBoy \"...No... I was born here, just like all the other bird friends. Can't you tell? / ……不对……我就是在这里出生的，就像其他所有的鸟儿朋友。你看不出来吗？\"/pause 800/quickQuestion #If you're a bird, how can you speak?#How old are you?(break)showFrame ParrotBoy 16\\jump ParrotBoy\\pause 1700\\showFrame ParrotBoy 0\\pause 500\\addTemporaryActor Toddler 13 10 7 4 2 true Parrot\\hideShadow Toddler true\\specificTemporarySprite parrotHutSquawk\\faceDirection farmer 0 true\\faceDirection ParrotBoy 0 true\\textAboveHead Toddler \"*Awk* / （叽叽喳喳）\"\\pause 1000\\textAboveHead Toddler \"If you're a bird\"\\pause 1500\\specificTemporarySprite parrotHutSquawk\\textAboveHead Toddler \"*Awk*\"\\pause 1000\\textAboveHead Toddler \"How can you speak?\"\\pause 1700\\animate ParrotBoy false true 150 17 22\\jump ParrotBoy\\pause 400\\speak ParrotBoy \"Haha! See? We speak! We speak!$h\"(break)pause 400\\speak ParrotBoy \"Old?$s#$b#...We don't think like that.#$b#We say... 'How many golden walnuts have you eaten?'$h#$b#...I've eaten 3,729 golden walnuts.#$b#...But you don't become an elder until you've eaten 10,000.$s#$b#I'll get there someday!$h\"/pause 500/emote farmer 28/move farmer 0 2 2/stopAnimation ParrotBoy/faceDirection ParrotBoy 2 true/textAboveHead ParrotBoy \"Hey. / 嘿。\"/pause 1000/faceDirection farmer 0/speak ParrotBoy \"...I remembered something.$s / ……我想起来了。$s\"/emote farmer 8/speak ParrotBoy \"My name...$s / 我的名字……$s\"/translateName ParrotBoy Strings\\NPCNames:Leo/speak ParrotBoy \"...It's Leo. / ……叫雷欧。\"/pause 500/emote farmer 32/end warpOut 2"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Events/IslandNorth",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "6497421/e 6497423/f Leo 1000/w sunny/t 600 1800/Hl leoMoved": "none/19 14/farmer 18 19 0 Leo 19 13 0/playMusic tropical_island_day_ambient/skippable/move farmer 0 -5 0/pause 1500/playSound parrot/shake Leo 500/pause 250/playSound batScreech/faceDirection farmer 2 true/startJittering/animate farmer false false 1000 94/jump farmer 8/pause 250/faceDirection Leo 2 true/animate Leo false false 1000 16/shake Leo 500/jump Leo 8/pause 250/stopJittering/faceDirection farmer 0 true/pause 3000/speak Leo \"Sorry...$u / 对不起……$u\"/speak Leo \"It's hard to remember to talk... normally...$s / 想记得正常地说话……有点难……$s\"/pause 500/emote Leo 40/pause 1000/speak Leo \"You think I'm weird, don't you?$s / 你有没有觉得我很怪？$s\"/quickQuestion #Not at all#A little, but I'm used to it#(Squawk loudly)(break)pause 250\\speak Leo \"Thanks for saying that. / 谢谢你这么说。\"(break)pause 250\\speak Leo \"Thanks, I've gotten used to you too!$h\"(break)pause 250\\startJittering\\playSound parrot\\pause 250\\stopJittering\\pause 250\\speak Leo \"Hehe... You're getting pretty good at that!$h\"/viewport move 0 -1 4000/pause 500/faceDirection Leo 1 true/pause 500/faceDirection Leo 0 true/pause 1000/playMusic sad_kid/pause 4000/speak Leo \"Sometimes I wonder how different my life would be if I had never washed up on this island...$s / 我有时会想，如果我没有被海浪带到这个岛上，我的生活会有什么不同……$s\"/pause 3000/speak Leo \"Back home, I didn't really care about birds. I never thought to listen to what they might be saying.$s / 在故乡的时候，我根本就不在意小鸟。我从没注意听过它们在说什么。$s\"/pause 1000/emote Leo 40/pause 2000/speak Leo \"Though I guess that's normal for... normal kids.$s / 虽说我觉得这很正常，对于……正常的孩子来说。$s\"/pause 1000/faceDirection Leo 1 true/pause 1000/speak Leo \"I wonder what... normal kids would have to say about me...$s / 我不知道……正常的孩子会怎么评论我……$s\"/pause 1000/emote Leo 40/pause 1000/faceDirection Leo 2 true/pause 500/speak Leo \"Do you think I could ever be a normal kid again?$s / 你觉得我能变回一个正常的孩子吗？$s\"/question null \"#Yes#No#Maybe... / #能#不能#也许能……\"/pause 1000/speak Leo \"Hmmm... I guess you're right.$u / 唔……也许你说得对。$u\"/speak Leo \"Though living on this island has given me a lot of experiences normal kids would never have.$h / 不过在这个岛上的生活让我经历了不少正常孩子不会接触的事情。$h\"/pause 1000/faceDirection Leo 0 true/pause 500/speak Leo \"If it weren't for the parrots... who knows what would have happened to me. / 要不是鹦鹉……谁知道我会怎么样呢。\"/pause 500/emote Leo 32/pause 500/speak Leo \"I'm happy I met them. I'll always consider them to be my family, even if that makes me a little strange.$h / 能遇到它们我很高兴。我会始终把它们当成我的家属，即使会显得我有点奇怪。$h\"/pause 500/viewport move 0 1 4000/pause 100/faceDirection Leo 2 true/move Leo 0 1 2/pause 250/faceDirection Leo 3/faceDirection farmer 1/pause 3000/speak Leo \"Anyways, thanks for talking to me, @. / 总之，谢谢你跟我聊天，@。\"/pause 500/speak Leo \"Maybe some day, you can be a part of our family too, hehe.$h / 也许有一天，你也会成为我们中的一员呢，哈哈。$h\"/pause 1000/faceDirection Leo 2 true/pause 1000/speak Leo \"Here, let me teach you how to say \\ / 来，我来教你“一起来玩”用鹦鹉语怎么说！\"Let's play\\\" in parrot talk!\"/pause 500/viewport move 0 1 99999/pause 500/playSound parrot/animate Leo false false 1000 17/shake Leo 1000/pause 2000/faceDirection farmer 2 true/startJittering/playSound parrot/pause 250/stopJittering/globalFade/viewport -5000 -5000/end"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Events/IslandSouth",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "PlayerKilled": "none/-100 -100/farmer 13 33 2 {0} 15 33 3/pause 1500/showFrame 5/message \" ...{2}? / ……{2}？\"/pause 1000/message \" {2}, wake up! / {2}，醒醒！\"/viewport 13 33 clamp true/pause 1000/speak {0} {1}/showFrame 0/pause 1000/emote farmer 28/minedeath/end",
        "IslandDepart": "none/-1000 -1000/farmer 15 43 2 Willy 17 45 2/playMusic none/skippable true/playSound furnace/beginSimultaneousCommand/viewport 16 44 clamp true/globalFadeToClear 0.007/endSimultaneousCommand/locationSpecificCommand boat_reset/locationSpecificCommand boat_depart/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/end islandDepart",
        "6497428/e 6497423/f Leo 1500/w sunny/t 600 1800/Hl leoMoved": "tropical_island_day_ambient/-1000 -1000/farmer 20 31 2 Leo 21 31 2 Willy -100 -100 1 Linus -100 -100 1/addConversationTopic LeoDeparture 0/skippable/move farmer 0 8 2 true/move Leo 0 5 2 true/viewport 21 38 true/proceedPosition Leo/emote Leo 8/speed Leo 4/move Leo 0 3 2 false/viewport move 0 1 2000/warp Willy 16 43/move Willy 1 0 1/warp Linus 16 43/move Willy 5 0 0/showFrame Leo 16/jump Leo/move Linus 4 0 0/showFrame Leo 0/shake Leo 1000/speed Leo 4/move Leo 0 -2 0/jump Linus/textAboveHead Linus \"Wait! / 等等！\"/pause 2700/faceDirection Leo 3 true/pause 100/faceDirection Leo 2/pause 1000/move Linus 0 -1 0/pause 1000/faceDirection Linus 1 true/pause 50/faceDirection Linus 2/showFrame Linus 26/pause 500/showFrame Linus 25/playSound parrot_squawk/shake Linus 500/pause 500/showFrame Linus 25/pause 600/showFrame Linus 0/pause 500/faceDirection Linus 1 true/pause 100/faceDirection Linus 0/pause 400/emote Leo 8/move Leo 0 1 2/pause 1000/animate Leo false true 500 17/playSound parrot_squawk/shake Leo 800/pause 1600/stopAnimation Leo/pause 500/emote Linus 32/move Linus 1 0 0/move Linus 0 -1 0/faceDirection Linus 1 true/pause 50/faceDirection Linus 2/showFrame Linus 26/pause 500/showFrame Linus 25/playSound parrot_squawk/shake Linus 500/pause 300/showFrame Linus 26/pause 400/showFrame Linus 25/playSound parrot_squawk/shake Linus 500/pause 500/showFrame Linus 25/pause 600/showFrame Linus 0/pause 500/faceDirection Linus 1 true/pause 100/faceDirection Linus 0/pause 400/jump Leo/pause 1000/move Leo 0 1 2/pause 500/speak Linus \"Hello, Leo... My name's Linus. / 你好，雷欧……我叫莱纳斯。#$b#I've heard all about you, and your parrot family. / 我听说了你的事情，包括你的鹦鹉家庭。#$b#It's really something special!$h / 真的很特别！$h\"/move Willy 0 -1 0/speak Willy \"Aye, lad... Linus lives on the mainland with the rest of us. / 对啊，小伙子……莱纳斯和我们其他人都生活在大陆上。#$b#After hearing your story... I wanted to help. So, I talked to Linus here and hatched a little plan.$h / 听到你的故事之后……我想帮帮你。所以，我跟莱纳斯谈了谈，想到了一个小小的计划。$h\"/playMusic ocean/pause 500/faceDirection Willy 3/speak Willy \"Go on, Linus... tell him. / 莱纳斯，继续吧……告诉他。\"/faceDirection Linus 1/pause 500/faceDirection Linus 0/faceDirection Willy 0/playMusic sad_kid/speak Linus \"Leo... / 雷欧……#$b#I'd like you to come back with us, to Stardew Valley. / 我想让你跟我们一起回星露谷去。#$b#It's a beautiful place... not as warm as here, but still full of life... and I live right in the middle of it! / 那个地方可漂亮了……没这里暖和，但是生机盎然……而且我住的地方就在正中心！#$b#I know the lay of the land, and many things about the waters, the trees, the animals, and more... / 我通晓那边的地形地貌，以及江湖、树木、动物，还有好多……#$b#You see... I'm a child of nature, too. You might say we're 'birds of a feather'.$h / 所以说……我也算是大自然的孩子，是同一类的。$h#$b#But, I'm getting old... And I'd like to teach someone all that I've learned before moving on...$s / 不过，我年岁已老……我想要在走之前把我学到的东西都传授给一个人……$s#$b#Leo... will you come back with us? / 雷欧……你愿意跟我们回去吗？\"/emote Leo 16/speak Leo \"L... leave the island?$u / 离……离开这座岛？$u\"/pause 600/speak Willy \"I can take you back for a visit any time!$h / 我可以随时带你回来看看的！$h#$b#But, lad.... You can't live here forever... / 但是，小伙子……你总不能在这里生活一辈子……#$b#You know, there are other children back home, too. I'm sure they'd love to meet ya... / 星露谷还有很多其他的孩子，他们肯定也盼望着见见你……\"/shake Leo 500/pause 700/speak Leo \"O... other kids?$u / 其……其他的孩子？$u\"/faceDirection Leo 3/pause 500/faceDirection Leo 2/speak Willy \"What do you think, @? / @，你觉得呢？\"/pause 400/quickQuestion #I think it's a great idea.#I think he should stay here.#It's up to Leo...(break)pause 400\\emote Willy 32\\speak Linus \"Well, let's not forget... the choice is really up to Leo... / 嗯，我们还是别忘了……最终还是要雷欧自己决定……\"\\pause 500(break)pause 100\\emote Willy 28\\speak Linus \"I understand. This is Leo's home, after all.$s\"\\move Linus -1 0 0\\speak Linus \"...It's hard to make changes. But sometimes it's for the best.#$b#Still... the choice is really up to Leo.\"(break)faceDirection farmer 1\\pause 400/faceDirection Leo 3/pause 400/faceDirection Leo 2/emote Leo 40/speak Leo \"I... $u / 我……$u#$b#I'll go... / 我跟你们走……\"/emote Willy 32 true/pause 400/textAboveHead Linus \"Great! / 太棒了！\"/pause 2000/faceDirection Leo 1 true/pause 100/faceDirection Leo 0/pause 300/emote Leo 28/pause 500/speak Leo \"But... my family...$s / 但是……我的家庭……$s\"/playMusic ocean/pause 2000/playSound parrot_squawk/pause 600/emote Leo 8/pause 700/playSound parrot_squawk/specificTemporarySprite BoatParrot/pause 2000/faceDirection Leo 3/jump Leo/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 3/faceDirection Linus 3 true/faceDirection Willy 3/pause 1000/speed Leo 4/move Leo 0 1 3/move Leo -1 0 3/pause 2000/specificTemporarySprite BoatParrotSquawk/pause 500/specificTemporarySprite BoatParrotSquawkStop/pause 600/specificTemporarySprite BoatParrotSquawk/pause 500/specificTemporarySprite BoatParrotSquawkStop/pause 1000/emote Leo 20/pause 500/speak Leo \"She says... / 她说……\"/pause 500/playMusic CloudCountry/faceDirection Leo 2/speak Leo \"She says the parrots are all happy for me. / 她说鹦鹉们对我感到高兴。#$b#...And that they want me to start the next chapter of life, wherever it may lead... / ……他们想让我开启生命的下一个篇章，无论前路如何……\"/pause 500/faceDirection Leo 3/speak Leo \"And no matter what happens... they'll always be my family... forever. / 而且无论发生什么……我都是家里的一员……永远。\"/pause 400/specificTemporarySprite BoatParrotSquawk/pause 500/specificTemporarySprite BoatParrotSquawkStop/pause 1000/specificTemporarySprite BoatParrotLeave/pause 500/speed Leo 4/move Leo 2 0 0/faceDirection farmer 0/faceDirection Linus 0 true/faceDirection Willy 0 true/textAboveHead Leo \"Goodbye! / 再见！\"/pause 5400/faceDirection Leo 1 true/pause 100/faceDirection Leo 2/emote Leo 40/pause 500/jump Leo/pause 500/speak Leo \"I'm ready!$h / 我准备好了！$h\"/faceDirection farmer 1/emote farmer 32 true/emote Willy 32 true/pause 1000/faceDirection Leo 3/pause 400/fade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 1300/message \"A new arrival to the valley... / 星露谷到来了一位新人……\"/pause 1200/message \"It seems our little town is growing! / 我们的小镇越来越热闹了！\"/pause 1000/end Leo"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Events/IslandWest",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "6497423/e 1039573/f Leo 500/w sunny/t 600 1800/Hl leoMoved": "sad_kid/79 89/farmer 79 89 2 Leo 80 81 2 Willy 89 87 3/skippable/move Leo 0 8 2/pause 200/faceDirection Leo 3/pause 600/faceDirection Leo 2/pause 1000/speak Leo \"What are you doing, @? / @，你在做什么？\"/pause 800/quickQuestion #Just enjoying the waves#Looking for fish#Thinking about someone special#Pondering the big questions(break)pause 500\\showFrame Leo 18\\emote Leo 28\\speak Leo \"Waves...$s / 海浪……$s#$b#The other birds say the reason Leo can't fly... is because Leo spend too much time in the waves, long ago.$s / 其他的鸟解释了为什么雷欧不能飞……是因为雷欧很久以前在海浪里面待得太久了。$s#$b#My wings full of water, now.$s / 我的翅膀现在充满了水。$s\"\\emote farmer 8(break)pause 500\\speak Leo \"Fish? Easy... $h#$b#If you want to say 'hi', you just have to ask.\"\\pause 500\\animate Leo false true 500 17\\playSound parrot_squawk\\shake Leo 800\\pause 800\\stopAnimation Leo\\pause 1200\\playSound pullItemFromWater\\specificTemporarySprite islandFishSplash\\animate farmer false true 100 94\\jump farmer\\pause 500\\animate Leo false true 150 17 22\\pause 2000\\stopAnimation farmer\\pause 1200\\stopAnimation Leo(break)pause 500\\faceDirection Leo 3\\emote Leo 8\\faceDirection Leo 2\\speak Leo \"Hmm... I don't understand that, yet.$s#$b#Maybe when I become an elder, someday.\"(break)pause 500\\speak Leo \"Oh.. Yeah. Leo ponders the big questions, too.\"\\faceDirection Leo 3\\speak Leo \"Like... 'will I find more walnuts on the beach, or in the volcano?'\"\\faceDirection Leo 2\\showFrame Leo 18\\emote Leo 28\\speak Leo \"*sigh*...Life complicated...$s\"/showFrame Leo 0/pause 1000/emote Leo 40/speak Leo \"@?$s / @？$s\"/pause 200/faceDirection farmer 1/speak Leo \"Tell me about the place you come from... your home.$s / 跟我讲讲你来的地方……你的家。$s\"/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 2/quickQuestion #There's a town full of people#There's forests, beaches, and mountains#It's like here, but colder#I live on a farm(break)emote Leo 40\\speak Leo \"People...$s / 人……$s\"(break)pause 400\\speak Leo \"Sounds nice.\"(break)emote Leo 8\\speak Leo \"Cold? ...I don't understand...$s\"(break)emote Leo 8\\speak Leo \"Farm? So, you're saying you grow your own walnuts? You don't have to hunt for them?$3#$b#...Wow..$3\"\\pause 500\\speak Leo \"I'm thinking... @ is smart.$h\"/pause 1500/showFrame Leo 18/playMusic ocean/pause 700/pause 1400/speak Leo \"Are... Are there... other kids?$s / 那里……那里有……其他小孩吗？$s\"/faceDirection farmer 1/pause 500/quickQuestion #Yes#What does that matter to a bird?(break)pause 100(break)pause 100/showFrame Leo 0/pause 1000/emote Leo 28/pause 600/faceDirection Leo 0/speak Leo \"...I know I'm not actually a bird, @...$s / ……@，我知道我实际上不是一只鸟……$s#$b#I'm like you.$s / 我跟你一样。$s#$b#But I don't like thinking about it...$s / 但是想到这些我不太舒服……$s#$b# ...because I'm so alone.$s / ……因为我太孤单了。$s\"/faceDirection Leo 3/speak Leo \"With my bird family, I feel like I belong.$s / 跟鸟的一家生活在一起，我有归属感。$s\"/pause 400/faceDirection Leo 2/showFrame Leo 18/pause 400/emote Leo 28/speak Leo \"But... I don't belong.$s / 但是……我并没有归属。$s#$b#...I don't belong anywhere...$s / ……我哪里都不属于……$s\"/speed Leo 4/faceDirection farmer 0 true/shake Leo 1000/move Leo 0 -9 0/move Willy -8 0 0/emote Willy 28/speak Willy \"Poor lad...$s / 可怜的孩子……$s\"/pause 500/speak Willy \"I wonder if there's some way to help...$s / 不知道有没有办法帮他……$s\"/pause 2000/fade/viewport -1000 -1000/end invisible Leo"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Events/JoshHouse",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "56/f Harvey 500/p George": "jaunty/16 18/farmer 9 24 0 George 16 18 1 Harvey 15 18 1/skippable/move farmer 0 -4 1/move farmer 1 0 1/speak Harvey \"Okay, George. I want you take a deep breath for me. / 好，乔治。我要你深吸一口气。\"/pause 700/speak Harvey \"Mmhmm... turn around, please. / 嗯……请转过身来。\"/pause 300/faceDirection George 2/faceDirection George 3/speak Harvey \"George, I'll be honest with you. You need to make some changes in your lifestyle if you want to stay healthy. / 乔治，我跟你说实话吧。你如果想健康长寿的话，就得改改你的生活方式。#$b#I'd like you to reduce your sodium intake, and try to get some moderate exercise with your arms. / 你得减少食盐的摄入量，并且适量锻炼一下你的手臂。\"/emote George 12/speak George \"Hmmph... I know what's best for me. Who do you think you are, telling me how to live my life? / 嗯……我知道怎么做最好。你以为你是谁啊，敢对我的生活指手画脚？\"/pause 500/speak Harvey \"I'm your doctor, George. That's who I am... / 你问我是谁……我是你的医生，乔治。#$b#And I went to school for 8 years so I could learn how to help people stay healthy. / 而我学了 8 年医，就是为了帮人们保持健康。\"/move farmer 0 -1 1/move farmer 5 0 0/faceDirection Harvey 2 true/faceDirection George 2/speak Harvey \"Oh! / 噢！#$b#I'm sorry, but you shouldn't be here... these check-ups are supposed to be private. / 对不起，你不能待在这里……检查时闲人免进。\"/faceDirection farmer 3/speak George \"Not so fast! I'd like to get a second opinion from this young man. / 别着急！我还要再听听这个年轻人的意见。^Not so fast! I'd like to get a second opinion from this young lady. / 别着急！我还要再听听这位年轻女士的意见。\"/faceDirection farmer 1/speak Harvey \"Very well... / 那好……\"/speak Harvey \"$q 84 null#@, what do you think George should do? / @你觉得乔治该怎么做？#$r 84 40 event_george1 friend_George_-20#George should follow Dr. Harvey's advice. / 乔治应该听从哈维医生的建议。#$r 84 40 event_george1 friend_George_-20#George knows what's best for his own body. / 乔治知道怎么做对他的身体最好。\"/faceDirection Harvey 1/faceDirection George 2/emote George 28/speak George \"Fine. I'll do what you say, doctor. / 好。我就照你说的做，医生。\"/pause 500/faceDirection Harvey 2/speak Harvey \"$p 84#Thanks for your help, @. I appreciate it.$h / 谢谢你的帮助，@。我很感激。$h|It's better not to give my patients mixed messages, @. Please remember that in the future. / 你最好不要误导我的病人，@。请你以后记住这一点。\"/end",
        "2119820/f Alex 1500/p Alex": "jaunty/-1000 -1000/farmer 10 10 0 Alex 13 6 2/skippable/showFrame Alex 28/animate Alex false true 100 28 29 30 31 32 32 31 30 29 28/viewport 13 6 true/pause 6500/stopAnimation Alex/pause 1000/doAction 10 9/move farmer 0 -3 1/move farmer 2 0 0/showFrame Alex 34 true/animate Alex false false 100 28 33 34/pause 600/speak Alex \"Oh! Hey... I was just doing my daily strength training routine.$6 / 噢！嘿……我正在进行日常体能锻炼。$6#$b#... sorry I have no shirt on.$6 / ……抱歉，我没有穿衬衫。$6\"/pause 1000/emote Alex 40/speak Alex \"Uh... @? I've been meaning to talk to you about something...$8 / @？我正想和你说件事儿呢……$8\"/emote farmer 8/pause 1000/speak Alex \"I've started to realize that... well, that I've been really rude towards you in the past. You know, about going pro and all that.$8 / 我已经开始意识到……那个，我以前对你太粗鲁了。就是关于去职业队的事情。$8\"/pause 1000/showFrame Alex 33/pause 1000/speak Alex \"I guess I might not actually be cut out for professional sports... maybe it was just a childish dream... you know?$8 / 我想我其实不是做专业运动员的料……或许那只是我幼稚的幻想……你说呢？$8#$b#Anyway... I want to apologize to you for bragging and being annoying about it. I appreciate that you stayed friends with me through all that.$6 / 话说……我想为我的夸夸其谈和喋喋不休，向你道歉。谢谢你不生我的气，还把我当作朋友。$6\"/move farmer 1 0 0/pause 1000/jump farmer/pause 800/showFrame Alex 34/pause 800/emote Alex 32/pause 1200/showFrame Alex 29/pause 100/showFrame Alex 28/pause 100/showFrame Alex 29/pause 100/animate Alex false true 50 30 31 32 32 31 30/pause 3000/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/end",
        "21/f Alex 1250/p Alex": "sadpiano/12 5/farmer 10 11 0 Alex 13 5 0/skippable/pause 500/speak Alex \"*sigh*$s / *唉*$s\"/doAction 10 9/move farmer 0 -5 1/move farmer 3 0 0/pause 500/faceDirection Alex 2/pause 600/speak Alex \"Oh, Hi @.$s / 哦，嗨，@。$s\"/faceDirection Alex 0/move farmer 1 0 0/move farmer 0 -1 3/emote farmer 8/pause 500/emote Alex 28/speak Alex \"Look at all these books. I haven't read a single one. Just the thought of cracking one open makes me nervous.$s / 瞧瞧这些书啊。我一本都没读过。光是想到要把书翻开，就让我紧张得不行。$s#$b#But you can't make a decent living in this world without a brain...$s / 但在这个世上，没有文化，就过不上好日子……$s\"/faceDirection Alex 1/speak Alex \"$q 57 null#I'm worthless...$s / 我真没用……$s#$r 57 0 Event_books1#That's crazy. You're a genius! / 才不是。你明明是个天才！#$r 57 50 Event_books2#We all have our strengths and weaknesses. / 我们都有自己的长处和短处。#$r 57 -50 Event_books3#Worthless? Yeah, that about sums it up. / 没用？对，总结得很精辟。\"/faceDirection Alex 0/pause 1000/emote Alex 16/speak Alex \"Well, I'm not going to give up!$a / 好吧，我不会放弃！$a\"/faceDirection Alex 1/speak Alex \"If I work hard, I can do anything! / 有志者事竟成！\"/jump farmer/pause 800/speak Alex \"Hey, maybe one day soon we'll have dinner and discuss ....phi-lo-so-phy. Isn't that what you smart people talk about?$h / 嘿，说不定我们很快就能一边吃饭一边讨论……则、哲、哲学。你们聪明人经常谈论的就是这个吧？$h\"/faceDirection farmer 2/animate farmer false true 100 102 103/pause 2000/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/stopAnimation farmer/end",
        "19/f Evelyn 1000/p Evelyn": "jaunty/3 17/farmer 8 19 3 Evelyn 3 17 0/skippable/move farmer -5 0 0/move farmer 0 -1 0/emote farmer 8/faceDirection Evelyn 2/speak Evelyn \"Oh! @! You're wondering what that good smell is? / 噢！@!你是不是在想这阵香味儿是从哪儿飘来的啊？#$b#Why, that's nice of you to say! I'm actually baking my famous cookies!$h / 哈哈，你真会说话！我其实正在烤我的招牌饼干！$h\"/emote farmer 16/speak Evelyn \"Here, why don't you try one? / 给，尝尝味道怎么样？\"/faceDirection Evelyn 0/pause 600/playSound clank/pause 600/faceDirection Evelyn 2/pause 900/farmerEat 223/pause 2000/stopAnimation farmer/faceDirection farmer 0/speak Evelyn \"$q 51 null#Well, what do you think? / 您觉得如何？#$r 51 100 Event_cookies1#It's delicious! / 很美味！#$r 51 -100 Event_cookies2#It was like chewing on a hockey puck / 就像在嚼冰球\"/playMusic none/speak Evelyn \"I think I've come to know you well enough to give you my recipe. Just make sure to keep it a secret.$h / 既然我们已经这么熟了，就把我的配方给你吧。但是你要保守秘密。$h\"/playSound reward/message \"Learned how to make 'Cookies' / 已学会制作“饼干”\"/addCookingRecipe Cookies/end",
        "18/f George 1500/p George": "sadpiano/17 17/farmer 10 19 1 George 18 17 0/skippable/emote George 12/speak George \"Nnnnggghh....I just can't reach it!$u / 不行……够不到！$u#$b#If only I could get up from this infernal chair...$s / 要是我能从这该死的椅子上站起来……$s\"/move farmer 4 0 0/move farmer 0 -2 0/move farmer 3 0 0/pause 500/showFrame 15/pause 500/pause 500/playSound Ship/pause 500/stopAnimation farmer/faceDirection farmer 1/faceDirection George 3/showFrame 35/pause 500/playSound coin/pause 300/stopAnimation farmer/pause 500/speak George \"Thanks, young man. / 谢谢你，年轻人。^Thanks, miss. / 谢谢\"/pause 800/speed George 1/faceDirection George 2/pause 500/move George 0 1 2/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 1000/speak George \"*sigh*...It happened 30 years ago.$s / 孩子，那是 30 年前。$s#$b#I was working in the coal mines. We were near the end of our shift, but there was one last seam that needed to be broken up. / 我当时在煤矿里上班。我们马上就要换班了，但还剩最后一个矿需要炸开。#$b#I went in there aiming to set off a stick of dynamite, but my foot slipped into a crack and I dropped it. The dynamite exploded on impact. / 我拿着一支炸药，要去引爆，但我绊了一下。炸药掉在地上，爆炸了。\"/pause 800/speak George \"The next thing I remember, I was laying in the hospital... and they told me I'd never walk again. / 等我再醒过来的时候，就已经躺在医院里了……然后他们告诉我，我再也不能走路了。\"/faceDirection George 3/speak George \"So there you have it. You probably figured I was just too old to walk. / 你明白了吧。你本来以为我是因为太老所以不能走路的吧#$b#Well I'll have you know that I'd be spryer than a spring chicken if I hadn't been in that accident! / 如果不是那场意外，现在我的腿脚肯定比年轻还灵活！\"/faceDirection George 2/speak George \"... / ……\"/move farmer 0 1 1/pause 1700/speak George \"You've been very nice to me, young man. I appreciate that. / 你对我很好，年轻人。非常感谢。^You've been really nice to me, miss. I appreciate it. / 你对我真的不错，孩子。我很感激。#$b#When you're old, you start to forget that anyone cares about you. / 等你老了，就会开始忘记，所有人都在关心你。\"/pause 800/faceDirection George 3/pause 1000/end",
        "5837189/n georgeGifts": "jaunty/-1000 -1000/farmer -100 -100 02 George 18 19 2 Evelyn 3 17 0/skippable/animate George false true 400 0 20/positionOffset George 0 -16/specificTemporarySprite staticSprite LooseSprites\\\\Cursors2 114 241 14 15 17 17/specificTemporarySprite staticSprite LooseSprites\\\\Cursors2 114 241 14 15 19.5 18.5/specificTemporarySprite staticSprite LooseSprites\\\\Cursors2 114 241 14 15 16.5 18/specificTemporarySprite staticSprite LooseSprites\\\\Cursors2 114 241 14 15 20 17/specificTemporarySprite staticSprite LooseSprites\\\\Cursors2 114 241 14 15 19 17/specificTemporarySprite staticSprite LooseSprites\\\\Cursors2 103 243 10 13 18.5 19.5/specificTemporarySprite staticSprite LooseSprites\\\\Cursors2 114 241 14 15 17.25 20.6/specificTemporarySprite staticSprite LooseSprites\\\\Cursors2 114 241 14 15 17 21 999 .8/specificTemporarySprite staticSprite LooseSprites\\\\Cursors2 114 241 14 15 17.5 21 999 .8/specificTemporarySprite staticSprite LooseSprites\\\\Cursors2 103 243 10 13 15 18/specificTemporarySprite staticSprite LooseSprites\\\\Cursors 288 1231 16 16 17 19 998/viewport 18 19 true/pause 5000/warp farmer 9 24/playSound doorClose/move farmer 0 -4 1/move farmer 4 0 1/stopAnimation George/faceDirection George 3/speak George \"@? What's the meaning of all this... / @？这都是什么意思……#$b#Is this some kind of prank? / 是什么恶作剧吗？\"/pause 500/quickQuestion #We wanted to show our appreciation#Your wife set this up#Yes, it's a prank(break)playMusic none\\pause 1000\\positionOffset George -4 0\\playSound Cowboy_Footstep\\pause 500\\positionOffset George -4 0\\playSound Cowboy_Footstep\\pause 500\\positionOffset George -4 0\\playSound Cowboy_Footstep\\pause 500\\specificTemporarySprite georgeLeekGift\\specificTemporarySprite removeSprite 998\\playSound Ship\\pause 800\\showFrame George 21\\playSound coin\\playMusic echos\\pause 1000\\speak George \"Leek... $s / 韭葱……$s\"\\pause 1000\\speak George \"My favorite... Just like Mama used to make, so many years ago...\"\\pause 2000\\showFrame George 0\\faceDirection George 2\\speak George \"Hmmph. Well...\"\\emote George 40\\showFrame George 16\\pause 500\\speak George \"Well... That... Hmmph.#$b#I guess maybe I'm not as forgotten and ignored as I thought...$s\"\\faceDirection George 3\\speak George \"Thanks, son.$h^Thanks, hun.$h#$b#You made an old man's day.$h\"\\pause 500\\emote farmer 32(break)playMusic none\\pause 300\\jump George\\pause 1000\\speak George \"Hah! She thought she could fool me!\"\\pause 500\\faceDirection George 2\\pause 400\\showFrame George 16\\pause 600\\speak George \"She thought she could fool me... into thinking I'm anything more than an inconvenience.$s\"\\stopAnimation George\\faceDirection George 3\\speak George \"Well, I know better...\"\\pause 400\\faceDirection George 1\\speak George \"Now, scram!$u\"\\emote farmer 28(break)playMusic none\\pause 300\\jump George\\pause 1000\\speak George \"Hah! You're a prankster, then?\"\\emote George 40\\playMusic playful\\speak George \"Hahah... You know, I was a bit of a prankster back in the day, too.$h\"\\faceDirection George 2\\speak George \"Well, at least you gave me a laugh.$h\"\\pause 2000\\faceDirection George 3\\emote George 8\\speak George \"What, you think I'm going to open them?\"\\jump George\\pause 1000\\speak George \"Hah! Not a chance. You think I'd fall for the old 'exploding present' gag?\"\\faceDirection George 2\\speak George \"These are going straight into the trash!\"\\pause 300\\faceDirection farmer 2 true\\showFrame farmer 94\\jump farmer/pause 2000/end"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Events/LeahHouse",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "584059/f Leah 2000/p Leah/n LeahInternet": "breezy/-1000 -1000/farmer 7 9 0 Leah 12 10 2/skippable/specificTemporarySprite leahLaptop/showFrame Leah 28/positionOffset Leah 0 12/viewport 11 9/move farmer 0 -1 1/move farmer 4 0 2/showFrame Leah 29/speak Leah \"Hey! Come check this out. / 嘿！看这个。\"/pause 500/showFrame Leah 28/move farmer 0 2 2/pause 400/speak Leah \"I bought a laptop and set up an online art shop... like you suggested. / 我买了一台笔记本电脑，在网上开了个艺术品商店……就像你建议的那样。\"/pause 800/playSound Pickup_Coin15/showFrame Leah 29/pause 400/speak Leah \"Did you hear that? That means someone just bought something from the store!$h / 你听到了吗？这代表刚刚有人买了件东西！$h\"/showFrame Leah 28/emote Leah 40/speak Leah \"Hmm... There's this 'Mr. K' that keeps buying all my sculptures.$7 / 嗯……嗯……就是这个“K 先生”一直在买我的雕像。$7#$b#I guess it must be some rich guy who loves my stuff. / 我想他一定是个有钱人，刚好又很喜欢我的作品。\"/pause 500/playSound Pickup_Coin15/pause 300/emote Leah 16/speak Leah \"Wow! I'm not going to have to worry about my electricity bill for a while after that sale...$6 / 哇！自从那促销之后，现在我暂时不用担心我的电费单了……$6\"/pause 800/showFrame Leah 29/speak Leah \"Anyway... Thanks for giving me this idea, @. So far, it's been really successful! This is really going to give me the funding I need to keep working on art full-time.$h / 话说……感谢你给我出的这个主意，@。目前来看，这确实是个大成功！这样我就有钱去进行全职的艺术创作了。$h\"/showFrame Leah 28/speak Leah \"Now, sorry to ignore you... but I really need to tweak these CSS sheets...$7 / 对不起，我要失陪一下……我得先整整这些 CSS 表单……$7\"/pause 500/playSound Pickup_Coin15/pause 1000/playSound Pickup_Coin15/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/end warpOut",
        "angry": "emote Leah 12/faceDirection Leah 1/speak Leah \"Sorry... I shouldn't get angry.$s / ……抱歉。我不该发火。$s\"/emote Leah 40/speak Leah \"Maybe you're right... my life would've been a lot easier if I had stayed.$u / 或许你是对的……如果我留在那里，生活应该容易得多。$u#$b#Maybe it's better to be practical and realistic... for all I know my art career will never pan out and I'll live my final years in squalor.$s / 也许还是现实一点儿的好……在我看来，我的艺术生涯永远不会成功，最后我只能在悲惨的境遇中结束自己的一生。$s\"/pause 500/faceDirection Leah 3/pause 500/speak Leah \"Well, thanks for listening to me. It's good to have a friend. / 好吧，感谢你能听我说完。有朋友的感觉真好。\"/pause 1500/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/end warpOut",
        "internet": "speak Leah \"Hmm... I guess that's an idea... But I'd need a computer first.$7 / 嗯……我想这是个办法……但我得先搞台电脑。$7\"/addMailReceived LeahInternet/faceDirection Leah 3/emote Leah 28/pause 500/speak Leah \"And again... that's expensive.$s / 但……那可不便宜啊。$s\"/pause 1000/speak Leah \"Well, it was nice of you to visit... / 好吧，感谢你的拜访……\"/pause 600/move farmer 4 0 2 true/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/end warpOut",
        "artShowSuggest": "pause 50/speak Leah \"Anyway... I've been thinking a little more about that art show idea you had. / 话说……我一直在考虑你说的那个开艺术展的事情。#$b#I'm working on some new sculptures to display at the show... I'm nervous, but the thought of getting my work out there is pretty exciting. / 我制作了几尊新雕像，想在艺术展上展出……我很紧张，但想到能展示自己的作品也好兴奋。#$b#I'm just glad you're on board with making Stardew Valley a premier art destination, @!$h / 很高兴你愿意和我一起从星露谷开始，@！$h\"/pause 500/end warpOut",
        "creepySexualPass": "stopMusic/faceDirection farmer 2/speed Leah 4/move Leah 1 0 0/speed Leah 4/move Leah 0 -1 3/animate Leah false false 100 16 17 18 19/pause 100/playSound ow/playSound clubhit/animate farmer false false 1200 94/positionOffset farmer -8 0/pause 50/positionOffset farmer 8 0/pause 800/stopAnimation farmer/pause 100/end dialogueWarpOut Leah \"...$a\"",
        "internet2": "pause 50/speak Leah \"So I've been saving up money to buy a computer... You know, so I can try and sell my art online like you suggested. / 我一直在存钱买电脑……然后我就能按照你的建议，在网上出售我的作品。\"/emote farmer 32/speak Leah \"It's good to have a friend looking out for you! / 有朋友关心，真是太好了！\"/pause 1500/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/end warpOut",
        "50/f Leah 500/p Leah": "breezy/9 8/farmer -50 -50 0 Leah 3 7 3/skippable/animate Leah false true 100 16 17 18 19 19 19 19 16/pause 100/playSound woodyStep/pause 800/playSound woodyStep/pause 800/playSound woodyStep/pause 800/warp farmer 7 9/playSound woodyStep/playSound doorClose/pause 300/stopAnimation Leah/pause 300/faceDirection Leah 1 true/emote Leah 16/speak Leah \"Oh, hi @! Come in, come in. / 啊，你好，@！快进来，快进来。\"/move farmer 0 -2 3/faceDirection Leah 1/move farmer -2 0 3/pause 500/speak Leah \"I'm just working on this sculpture here. / 我正在加工这座雕像。\"/pause 300/speak Leah \"Come here. Watch this. / 过来看看吧。\"/pause 300/move farmer -1 0 3/move farmer 0 -1 0/move farmer -1 0 2/faceDirection Leah 3/pause 500/animate Leah false true 100 16 17 18 19 19 19 19 16/pause 100/playSound woodyStep/pause 800/playSound woodyStep/pause 800/playSound woodyStep/pause 800/playSound woodyStep/pause 600/stopAnimation Leah/showFrame Leah 19/speak Leah \"See that? I'm revealing the essence of the wood. / 看到了吗？我正在揭示木头的本质。\"/pause 500/showFrame Leah 12/faceDirection Leah 0/speak Leah \"$q -1 null#Once you get past the outer layers, the true nature starts to show... / 等剥去了外层之后，真实的本性才开始展现……#$r -1 0 event_sculpt1#It's the same with people. / 人也是这样。#$r -1 0 event_sculpt2#I actually prefer the look of raw, unadulterated wood. / 我其实更喜欢未经雕琢的木头。#$r -1 -100 event_sculpt3#(creepy) May I have a kiss? / （唐突）你能亲我一下吗？\"/fork creepySexualPass/faceDirection Leah 3/pause 1500/faceDirection Leah 3/speak Leah \"I first visited this valley as a little girl, while on vacation with my parents. / 我第一次和父母来这座山谷度假的时候，还是个小姑娘。#$b#I knew I had to come back some day... This place has great artistic potential! / 我知道，总有一天我会回来……这个地方充满了艺术气息！\"/faceDirection Leah 3/pause 500/emote Leah 28/speak Leah \"Although, I have to admit... It's not easy to pay the bills as an artist.$s / 但我得承认……作为艺术家，想要养活自己可不容易。$s\"/pause 1000/emote farmer 16/faceDirection Leah 0/question fork1 \"#Why don't you have an art show in town?#Why don't you sell your art on the internet? / #你为啥不在镇上举办一个艺术展呢？#你为啥不把你的作品放在网上出售啊？\"/fork internet/faceDirection Leah 0/speak Leah \"Hmmm... interesting. I guess that could set the wheels in motion to making Pelican Town a true art destination...$7 / 嗯……有意思。我想这可能会帮助鹈鹕镇变成真正的艺术之乡……$7\"/faceDirection Leah 3/pause 700/speak Leah \"But what if no one likes my sculptures? I'd be crushed.$s / 但如果没人喜欢我的雕像呢？那我就完了。$s\"/pause 500/speak Leah \"...I'll have to think about it.$s / 这我得考虑一下。$s\"/faceDirection Leah 0/speak Leah \"Well, thanks for stopping by, @. / 好吧，感谢你的拜访，@。\"/pause 600/move farmer 4 0 2 true/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/addMailReceived LeahArtShowSuggestion/end dialogueWarpOut Leah \"An art show for the whole village? That's a bold idea, @.\"",
        "51/f Leah 1000/p Leah": "sadpiano/-1000 -1000/farmer 7 9 0 Leah 13 8 0/skippable/showFrame Leah 20/changeMapTile Front 14 7 1453/viewport 12 8/move farmer 0 -1 1/speak Leah \"Kel...How many times do I have to tell you? I don't want to come back to the city!$8 / 凯尔……还要我跟你说多少次？我不想回城里去！$8#$b#Stop calling me... I don't want to hear from you anymore! *click*$8 / 别再给我打电话了……我再也不想听到你的声音了！*挂断*$8\"/playSound openBox/faceDirection Leah 1/changeMapTile Front 14 7 1454/emote Leah 12/pause 1000/move farmer 4 0 1/faceDirection Leah 3/speak Leah \"@...$6 / @……$6\"/pause 300/emote Leah 28/speak Leah \"So I guess you heard me yelling on the phone?$s / 我猜你听到我对着电话大喊大叫了？$s\"/faceDirection Leah 2/move farmer 1 0 1/pause 1000/playMusic desolate/speak Leah \"That was my ex...$s / 那是我的前……$s\"/faceDirection Leah 3/emote farmer 16/pause 600/speak Leah \"I guess I'd better tell you a little about it...$u / 我最好还是稍微和你解释一下吧……$u\"/pause 500/faceDirection Leah 2/pause 500/speak Leah \"We had an apartment together, back in the city.$u / 我们一起在城里租了一间公寓。$u#$b#I did odd jobs during the day and spent all night working on art projects... we barely made enough to scrape by.$u / 我白天要打零工，晚上则要通宵制作艺术品……我们的收入只够勉强度日。$u#$b#${He^She}$ was always nagging me to go back to school and study business or medicine... something with a lot of money in it.$a / ${他^她}$一直在唠叨我，要我回学校，去学习商业或是医学……那都是挣钱的职业。$a#$b#I guess the idea was to save up for a normal life. You know... a house in the suburbs, kids, PTA meetings... that sort of thing.$u / 我觉得那是一般人的活法。你知道的……就是在郊区买房、生孩子、开家长会……之类的事情。$u\"/faceDirection Leah 3/speak Leah \"I wasn't ready for that kind of life, @... I had to leave. So I came here to pursue my dream of being an artist. / 我还没有过那种生活的打算，@……我非离开不可。所以我才会来这儿，追寻成为艺术家的梦想。\"/pause 900/faceDirection Leah 2/speak Leah \"$q 83 null#Was that selfish of me, @?$s / 我是不是太自私了，@?$s#$r 83 0 event_parents1#No, it had to be done. / 不，你只是做了必须做的事情。#$r 83 0 event_parents2#No, and your ex sounds like an idiot. / 不，是你的前任太蠢了。#$r 83 -20 event_parents3#No, but you would've been better off staying in the city. / 不，但你其实应该待在城里。#$r 83 -20 event_parents4#Yeah, a little. / 对，有那么一点儿。#$r 83 -20 event_parents5#Yeah, but it's natural to care about yourself first. / 对，但人不为己天诛地灭。\"/faceDirection Leah 3/fork angry/pause 200/fork LeahInternet internet2/fork LeahArtShowSuggestion artShowSuggest/speak Leah \"Well, thanks for listening to me. It's good to have a friend. / 好吧，感谢你能听我说完。有朋友的感觉真好。\"/pause 1500/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/end dialogueWarpOut Leah \"Hey, thanks for listening to me so patiently earlier.\""
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Events/ManorHouse",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "prizeTicketIntro/n completedFirstBillboardQuest": "distantBanjo/3 6/farmer -2000 -2000 0 Lewis 1 6 0/skippable/pause 2000/warp farmer 5 11/playSound doorClose/pause 400/move farmer 0 -5 0/move farmer -3 0 3/pause 400/faceDirection Lewis 1/pause 500/emote Lewis 16/speak Lewis \"Ah, hello there, @. / 你好啊，@。\"/pause 500/faceDirection Lewis 0/speak Lewis \"I was just loading some more prizes into this machine here... / 我刚刚往兑奖机里又装了一些奖品……\"/pause 300/faceDirection farmer 0/emote farmer 8/pause 500/speak Lewis \"It's a new program I've come up with, to help promote a spirit of goodwill among the townsfolk... You included! / 这是我想出来的一个新项目，目的在于增进镇民之间的善意……包括你在内！#$b#It's pretty simple... sometimes, when you help out others in town, you'll receive a 'Prize Ticket'. You can turn them in for rewards. / 流程很简单……你在镇上帮助别人的时候，偶尔可以收到“兑奖券”，拿到这里就可以兑奖。#$b#There's some special stuff in there!$h / 有一些特别奖品哦！$h\"/pause 500/emote farmer 56/faceDirection Lewis 1/emote Lewis 40/speak Lewis \"My only worry is that people will just go after the tickets, rather than cultivating a true compassion for their fellow man...$s / 我唯一担心的是会有人只为了获得兑奖券，而不是真正热心对待其他人……$s\"/faceDirection farmer 3/quickQuestion #I just want to help.#Yep, I'm in it for the prizes.(break)pause 100\\emote Lewis 32\\speak Lewis \"Is that so? Well, I'm glad to hear that!$h / 是吗？那太好了！$h\"(break)pause 50\\jump Lewis\\pause 500\\speak Lewis \"I see!$u#$b#Well... that's not what I hoped to hear, but I appreciate the honesty.\"/pause 500/speak Lewis \"At any rate... keep checking the 'Help Wanted' board in town. That's a good way to get your hands on more tickets. / 不管怎样……请你多多关注镇上的求助板，这样可以拿到更多兑奖券。#$b#Good luck out there. / 祝你好运。\"/pause 500/end",
        "2123243/e 2111194": "EmilyTheme/-1000 -1000/farmer -2000 -2000 0 Emily 7 6 2 Lewis 3 7 1 Clint 11 9 3 Shane 8 8 0 Abigail 7 8 0 Robin 2 9 1/skippable/specificTemporarySprite ClothingTherapy/viewport 5 7 true/pause 2000/speak Emily \"Welcome to clothing therapy! / 欢迎来到服装疗法！\"/faceDirection Abigail 1/emote Robin 8 true/faceDirection Shane 3/pause 500/faceDirection Shane 0/faceDirection Abigail 0/pause 500/speak Emily \"You're probably wondering... what is clothing therapy? / 你可能想知道……什么是服装疗法？#$b#I'll try to explain. / 我会试着解释。\"/move Emily 0 1 2/speak Emily \"So many of us are struggling with personal issues... things holding us back from living how we want.$u / 我们许多人都在与自身问题做斗争……这些东西阻碍我们过我们想要的生活。$u#$b#It's important to me that everyone has a free and happy life... so I came up with a new kind of therapy to help people achieve that.$u / 对我来说每个人都能拥有自由幸福的生活是很重要的……所以我提出一种新的疗法来帮助大家。$u\"/move Emily 0 -1 2/pause 500/speak Emily \"It's based on the amazing power of self-expression. Self-expression is a wonderful healing tool, did you know that? / 它基于自我表达这一神奇力量。自我表达是一种奇妙的治疗工具，你们知道吗？\"/faceDirection Emily 3/pause 1000/speak Emily \"Behind this curtain, you'll find racks and racks of clothes. There's endless options to choose from. / 在这块帘子后面，你会发现一货架一货架的衣服。有无尽的选择。\"/faceDirection Emily 2/speak Emily \"Your job is simple: find the outfit that truly speaks to you, and put it on. / 你需要做的事情很简单：找到适合你的衣服，然后穿上它。#$b#Feel confident in yourself and your choice. You all have a unique style to share with the world! / 要对你自己和你的选择有信心。分享给这个世界看属于你们独一无二的风格！#$b#Shane, you're up first!$h / 谢恩，你先来！$h\"/specificTemporarySprite curtainOpen/pause 1500/showFrame Shane 18/jump Shane/pause 1400/showFrame Shane 0/pause 1000/textAboveHead Shane \"Okay / 好\"/move Shane 0 -1 0/move Shane -3 0 0/move Shane 0 -2 2/pause 1000/specificTemporarySprite curtainClose/pause 1000/playSound doorClose/warp farmer 4 11/move farmer 0 -1 0/speak Emily \"Ah, @. You're just in time. Just observe and keep an open mind... okay? / 啊，@。你来的刚好。只需要观察和带着好奇的心态……好吗？\"/pause 1000/move farmer -1 0 0/warp Shane -1000 -1000/addTemporaryActor ClothesTherapyCharacters 16 32 5 5 2 true character/pause 3000/specificTemporarySprite curtainOpen/pause 1000/faceDirection Emily 3/move ClothesTherapyCharacters 0 2 2/textAboveHead Robin \"Wow... / 哇哦……\"/pause 1000/move ClothesTherapyCharacters 0 2 2/faceDirection Abigail 3/textAboveHead Abigail \"Cool / 酷\"/pause 1000/faceDirection Emily 2/speak Emily \"Shane, it's a new side of you we've never known about. That's great! / 谢恩，我们从来没有看过你这一面。太棒了！#$b#Now, go outside with confidence and show the world! / 现在走出去，自信点展示给这个世界看！\"/pause 1000/emote ClothesTherapyCharacters 40/pause 500/textAboveHead ClothesTherapyCharacters \"Sure / 当然\"/move ClothesTherapyCharacters 0 2 2/warp ClothesTherapyCharacters -1000 -1000/playSound doorClose/pause 2000/speak Emily \"Okay, everyone gets a turn! / 好吧，所有人都要试试！\"/faceDirection Abigail 0 true/move Robin 3 0 0/faceDirection Clint 2 true/textAboveHead Clint \"Oh no... / 哦不……\"/move Robin 0 -4 2/pause 1000/specificTemporarySprite curtainClose/pause 3000/warp Robin -1000 -1000/warp ClothesTherapyCharacters 5 5/changeYSourceRectOffset ClothesTherapyCharacters 128/textAboveHead ClothesTherapyCharacters \"Heehee / 天哪\"/pause 1000/specificTemporarySprite curtainOpen/pause 1000/textAboveHead Lewis \"Oh my! / 我的天哪！\"/move ClothesTherapyCharacters 0 3 2/textAboveHead Emily \"Beautiful! / 太漂亮了！\"/pause 1000/showFrame ClothesTherapyCharacters 5/specificTemporarySprite heart 5 8/pause 2000/textAboveHead ClothesTherapyCharacters \"Let's see what Demetrius thinks... / 我们看看德米特里厄斯怎么想……\"/pause 1000/move ClothesTherapyCharacters 0 3 2/warp ClothesTherapyCharacters -1000 -1000/playSound doorClose/pause 2000/textAboveHead Lewis \"Why not... / 为什么不……\"/move Lewis 2 0 0/move Lewis 0 -2 2/pause 1000/specificTemporarySprite curtainClose/faceDirection Emily 3/pause 2000/warp Lewis -1000 -1000/playSound shwip/warp ClothesTherapyCharacters 5 5/changeYSourceRectOffset ClothesTherapyCharacters 64/pause 1000/textAboveHead ClothesTherapyCharacters \"Hehe... not bad! / 嘿嘿……不错嘛！\"/pause 2000/specificTemporarySprite curtainOpen/pause 1000/move ClothesTherapyCharacters 0 3 2/textAboveHead Emily \"Lookin' sharp! / 快让我看看！\"/faceDirection Emily 2/pause 3000/move ClothesTherapyCharacters 0 3 2/playSound doorClose/warp ClothesTherapyCharacters -1000 -1000/textAboveHead Abigail \"Me next! / 下一个是我！\"/move Abigail -2 0 0/move Abigail 0 -3 2/pause 2000/specificTemporarySprite curtainClose/pause 2000/warp Abigail -1000 -1000/warp ClothesTherapyCharacters 5 5/changeYSourceRectOffset ClothesTherapyCharacters 32/pause 3000/specificTemporarySprite curtainOpen/pause 1000/move ClothesTherapyCharacters 0 3 2/textAboveHead Emily \"Very nice! / 很好！\"/pause 2000/showFrame ClothesTherapyCharacters 16/playSound clank/pause 1000/textAboveHead ClothesTherapyCharacters \"It's sweaty in here... / 这都出汗了……\"/pause 3000/move ClothesTherapyCharacters 0 3 2/warp ClothesTherapyCharacters -1000 -1000/playSound doorClose/pause 1000/faceDirection Emily 3/pause 500/faceDirection Emily 2/pause 1000/speak Emily \"Clint? You're up! / 克林特？到你了！\"/pause 500/jump Clint/shake Clint 4000/pause 1000/textAboveHead Clint \"M...Me? / 我……我吗？\"/pause 2000/speak Clint \"*gulp*... Okay, Emily. I'll do it.$4 / *咽口水*……好吧，艾米丽。我来了。$4\"/pause 1000/move Clint -6 0 0/move Clint 0 -4 2/pause 1000/faceDirection Emily 3/specificTemporarySprite curtainClose/pause 4000/warp Clint -1000 -1000/warp ClothesTherapyCharacters 5 5/changeYSourceRectOffset ClothesTherapyCharacters 96/pause 1000/specificTemporarySprite curtainOpen/pause 2000/move ClothesTherapyCharacters 0 3 2/faceDirection Emily 2/textAboveHead Emily \"Awww, cute! / 噢，真可爱！\"/pause 1600/showFrame ClothesTherapyCharacters 10/pause 800/speak Clint \"Aww? Cute? ...*sigh*...$7 / 噢？可爱？……*唉*……$7\"/pause 2000/move ClothesTherapyCharacters 0 3 2/warp ClothesTherapyCharacters -1000 -1000/playSound doorClose/move Emily 0 3 3/move farmer 0 -1 1/move farmer 1 0 1/speak Emily \"Well, that went very well! / 好吧，那很好！#$b#I just hope this experience helps everyone break out of their shells a bit. / 我只希望这些经验可以帮助每一个人突破他们的外形。\"/move Emily -2 0 3 true/pause 200/positionOffset Emily 0 4/pause 300/positionOffset Emily 0 4/pause 300/positionOffset Emily 0 4/pause 300/positionOffset Emily 0 4/pause 2500/speak Emily \"@... um...$4 / @……嗯……$4\"/showFrame ClothesTherapyCharacters 11/playSound doorClose/warp ClothesTherapyCharacters 5 11/speak Clint \"I couldn't do it! I don't wanna break out of my shell!$6 / 我不会改的！我不想突破我的外形！$6\"/faceDirection Emily 2 true/jump Emily/showFrame Emily 26/faceDirection farmer 2 true/pause 1600/showFrame Emily 0/speak Clint \"...Oh. I... I guess I'm interrupting something here, aren't I?$7 / ……哦。我……我想我打扰了你们，是吗？$7\"/pause 1000/showFrame ClothesTherapyCharacters 0/pause 1500/showFrame ClothesTherapyCharacters 10/pause 1700/speak Clint \"I understand. I'll leave now... Congrats, @.$7 / 我明白。我现在就离开……祝福你们，@。$7\"/pause 1000/playSound doorClose/warp ClothesTherapyCharacters -1000 -1000/pause 1000/faceDirection Emily 3/emote Emily 8/pause 2000/end"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Events/Mine",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "100162/t 600 2600": "MarlonsTheme/21 9/farmer -100 -100 0 Marlon 23 6 2/addQuest 14/skippable/pause 1000/move Marlon 0 2 2/pause 500/showFrame Marlon 4/pause 1000/speak Marlon \"Hmmm...  / 唔……\"/pause 500/warp farmer 18 13/playSound stoneStep/move farmer 0 -3 1/move farmer 5 0 0/pause 500/showFrame Marlon 0/pause 500/speak Marlon \"...I was just peering down into this old mine shaft. / 我只想看看这座古老的矿井。#$b#It's been abandoned for decades. / 它已经荒废几十年了。\"/pause 500/showFrame Marlon 4/speak Marlon \"Still, there's probably good ore down there. / 下面可能还有些不错的矿石。#$b#But a dark place, undisturbed for so long... I'm afraid ore isn't the only thing you'll find... / 但这么一个黑漆漆的地方，已经好久都没人下去过了……恐怕你能在那儿找到的不仅是矿石而已……\"/pause 500/showFrame Marlon 0/pause 500/speak Marlon \"Here, take this. You might need it. / 给，拿着这个。你兴许用得上。\"/pause 500/playSound dwop/faceDirection farmer 1 true/pause 50/faceDirection farmer 2/itemAboveHead sword/pause 3300/awardFestivalPrize sword/pause 300/faceDirection farmer 1 true/pause 100/faceDirection farmer 0/pause 500/speak Marlon \"Name's Marlon, by the way. I run the adventurer's guild right outside. / 顺便告诉你，我叫马龙。我就在外面经营着探险家公会。#$b#I'll keep my eye on you. Prove yourself and I might think about making you a member. / 我会关注着你的一举一动。如果你能证明自己，我可能会让你成为会员。\"/pause 500/end",
        "PlayerKilled": "none/-100 -100/farmer 19 10 2 {0} 18 10 1/pause 1500/showFrame 5/message \" ...{2}? /  ……{2}？\"/pause 1000/message \" {2}, wake up! /  {2}，醒醒！\"/viewport 19 10 true/pause 1000/speak {0} {1}/move {0} 0 3 2/warp {0} -100 -100/showFrame 0/pause 1000/emote farmer 28/minedeath/end",
        "901756/f Abigail 2500/t 1700 2400/o Abigail": "Upper_Ambient/18 7/farmer -1000 -1000 0 Abigail 18 11 0/skippable/move Abigail 0 -3 1/move Abigail 5 0 2/pause 500/animate Abigail false false 150 26 24 25 25 25 25/pause 450/playSound sandyStep/stopAnimation Abigail/showFrame Abigail 25/pause 2000/playSound batFlap/pause 500/playSound batFlap/pause 500/playSound batFlap/pause 500/emote Abigail 8/pause 1000/specificTemporarySprite abbyOneBat/playSound batScreech/showFrame Abigail 32/shake Abigail 2000/pause 2000/showFrame Abigail 0/pause 600/animate Abigail false true 100 28 29/pause 1200/stopAnimation Abigail/pause 1000/specificTemporarySprite abbyManyBats/showFrame Abigail 32/shake Abigail 2000/pause 2000/speed Abigail 8/move Abigail 0 -4 0/speed Abigail 8/move Abigail 2 0 0/animate Abigail false false 100 21 20 20/pause 200/showFrame Abigail 20/shake Abigail 10000/pause 2000/warp farmer 18 13/move farmer 0 -5 0/pause 1000/faceDirection farmer 1/pause 300/emote farmer 16/speed farmer 8/move farmer 6 0 0/speed farmer 8/playMusic desolate/move farmer 0 -4 1/speak Abigail \"$q 776589 null#*sniff*$s / *吸气*$s#$r 776589 20 Event_Cave2_1#What happened? / 发生了什么？#$r 776589 40 Event_Cave2_2#Are you okay? / 你还好吗？\"/pause 500/animate Abigail false false 100 21 0 0/pause 200/stopAnimation Abigail/faceDirection Abigail 3/pause 500/speak Abigail \"You know I've been practicing my swordsmanship for a while...$9 / 你也知道我练了一段时间的剑法……$9#$b#Well I decided today would be the day I venture into the caves...$8 / 所以我觉得今天是进山洞探险的好日子……$8\"/pause 500/faceDirection Abigail 1/pause 1000/speak Abigail \"...but I got scared. I couldn't do it.$8 / ……但我吓坏了。我做不到。$8\"/pause 500/faceDirection Abigail 3/speak Abigail \"$q 34 null#I guess I'm not as tough as I thought...$8 / 我可能没有自己想象的那么勇敢……$8#$r 34 20 Event_Cave_1#You're safe with me. / 和我在一起，你就安全了。#$r 34 40 Event_Cave_2#I get scared too. / 我也害怕。#$r 34 -50 Event_Cave_3#You're crying like a little baby. Stop. / 你哭得就像个三岁小孩儿。别说了。\"/faceDirection Abigail 3/stopMusic/pause 1500/playMusic sadpiano/pause 1800/speak Abigail \"@, I... I really like you... And not just as a friend. You know that, right?$l / @我……我真的喜欢你……不只是朋友间的那种喜欢。你懂我的意思吗？$l\"/pause 1000/speak Abigail \"I can't believe I'm actually saying this... But I can't keep it in anymore. I've felt this way for a long time.$l / 不敢相信，我居然会这么说……但我憋不住了。这种想法我已经在心里藏了好久。$l\"/pause 1800/speak Abigail \"You don't have to say anything right now. Let's just stay here for a while...$l / 你现在什么都不用说。就让我们在这儿待一会儿吧……$l^I didn't know I felt this way about other girls... until I met you. / 我从没对其他女孩儿有过这种感觉……直到我遇见了你。\"/playMusic Upper_Ambient/pause 1000/showFrame Abigail 33/showFrame 101/pause 2500/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/end"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Events/Mountain",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "8/f Maru 1500/w sunny/t 2100 2340": "nightTime/-1000 -1000/farmer 23 29 3 Maru 14 29 3/skippable/bgColor 0 0 0/changeToTemporaryMap NightSceneMaruMap false/ambientLight 0 0 0/viewport 14 23 true/pause 2000/playSound leafrustle/pause 200/faceDirection Maru 1/pause 400/emote Maru 8/pause 800/move farmer -5 0 3/speak Maru \"@! I'm surprised to see you here so late. / @！没想到这么晚，还能在这儿遇到你。\"/faceDirection Maru 3/pause 1000/speak Maru \"The night sky looks amazing right now. / 这会儿的夜空好美啊。\"/faceDirection Maru 1/speak Maru \"Come over here, I want to show you something. / 来，我想给你看样儿东西。\"/move farmer -3 0 3/speak Maru \"Here, take a peek. / 来，瞧一眼。\"/move Maru 0 1 0/move farmer -1 0 3/pause 200/animate farmer true true 100 35/pause 1200/playMusic spaceMusic/speak Maru \"$q 40 null#What do you see? / 你看到的是什么？#$r 40 30 Event_Space1#A beautiful planet. / 一颗美丽的星球。#$r 40 -30 Event_Space2#A cold, dark abyss. / 一片漆黑的深渊。\"/stopAnimation farmer/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 1000/speak Maru \"By the time any of these stars are visited, you and I will be long gone...$8 / 等人们能够登上这些星星的时候，你我早就不在人世了……$8\"/emote farmer 28/pause 400/speak Maru \"I guess that's the trouble with being human, huh? / 我想这就是身为人类所不好的一点，对不对？\"/faceDirection Maru 0/pause 1200/faceDirection Maru 2/emote Maru 40/pause 500/faceDirection Maru 0/speak Maru \"@, um...$8 / @，呃……$8\"/pause 500/faceDirection Maru 2/pause 1500/speak Maru \"Never mind...$s / 算了……$s\"/pause 500/faceDirection Maru 0/pause 800/speak Maru \"Here, let me show you a binary star system... / 来，我给你指双子星系……\"/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 3 true/animate farmer true true 100 35/pause 800/specificTemporarySprite maruTelescope/viewport move 0 -1 16000/pause 16000/globalFade .003/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 500/message \"What a beautiful night! Maru showed me something new... / 真是好美的夜晚啊！玛鲁让我见识了一些新东西……\"/pause 1000 /stopAnimation farmer/changeLocation Mountain/end",
        "404798/Hn ccFishTank": "spring_day_ambient/-1000 -1000/farmer 42 11 0 Willy 47 7 0/skippable/specificTemporarySprite dickBag/viewport 47 5 clamp true/emote Willy 8/move farmer 0 -4 1/move farmer 4 0 1/faceDirection Willy 3/pause 500/speak Willy \"Hi, @. / 嗨，@。\"/pause 500/faceDirection Willy 0/speak Willy \"It's odd... I'm not sure what caused this boulder to disappear. / 好奇怪……我不知道这块儿圆石是怎么消失的。\"/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 0/pause 500/speak Willy \"This stream is flowing from deep within the mountain. / 这条小溪的源头在深山里面。\"/pause 1000/specificTemporarySprite dickGlitter/playSound slosh/pause 500/faceDirection Willy 2/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 500/jump Willy/pause 800/emote Willy 16/speak Willy \"Hey! Do you see that glistening in the water? / 嘿！你看到水里那个闪闪发亮的东西了吗？\"/pause 800/showFrame Willy 24/pause 250/showFrame Willy 25/pause 1000/speak Willy \"Yes... that's quality ore!$h / 对……那是块优质矿石！$h\"/showFrame Willy 24/pause 200/showFrame Willy 0/pause 500/faceDirection Willy 3/speak Willy \"The flow of water must be carrying it out of the mountain. / 肯定是水流把它从山里带出来的。\"/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 1/pause 500/speak Willy \"You know what this means, right? / 你知道这意味着什么吗？\"/pause 900/jump Willy/pause 800/speak Willy \"It means we can start panning for ore!$h / 这意味着我们可以开始淘矿石了！$h\"/faceDirection Willy 2/faceDirection Willy 3/speak Willy \"Here, I've got an extra pan in my backpack... why don't you take it? / 给，我的背包里还有一个淘盘……你就用这个吧？\"/pause 800/faceDirection Willy 1/pause 800/showFrame Willy 26/pause 500/playSound coin/pause 500/showFrame Willy 4/pause 500/showFrame Willy 12/faceDirection Willy 3/awardFestivalPrize Pan/null/pause 800/faceDirection Willy 2/speak Willy \"If you ever see ore glistening in the water, use that pan and see what you find. / 只要在水里见到发光的矿石，就用淘盘捞上来看看。\"/faceDirection farmer 2/itemAboveHead pan/null/pause 1000/end",
        "371652/f Linus 2000/w sunny/t 600 1700/a 12 26": "sweet/18 32/farmer -1000 -1000 2 Robin -1000 -1000 2 Linus 23 33 1/skippable/animate Linus false true 250 20 21/pause 3000/doAction 24 33/pause 500/doAction 24 33/pause 800/doAction 24 33/pause 1000/stopAnimation Linus/move Linus -2 0 0/move Linus 0 -1 1/animate Linus false true 250 20 21/pause 500/doAction 22 32/pause 900/doAction 22 32/pause 200/doAction 22 32/pause 1200/stopAnimation Linus/move Linus -6 0 0/move Linus 0 -5 0 true/viewport move 0 -1 4000/move false/move Linus -2 0 3/warp Robin 12 26/playSound doorClose/pause 400/showFrame Robin 19/textAboveHead Robin \"Eep! / 呀！\"/shake Robin 500/pause 500/faceDirection Linus 0/showFrame Robin 0/pause 1 500/warp farmer 11 26/playSound doorClose/faceDirection Linus 3/pause 500/move farmer 0 1 1/pause 1000/speak Robin \"Oh... It's Linus, right?$s / 哦……是莱纳斯，对吧？$s\"/emote Robin 40/speak Robin \"Are you hungry? I could make you some lunch... How about some leftover cave carrot stew? / 你饿了吗？我可以为你做午饭……剩下的洞穴胡萝卜汤，怎么样？\"/pause 500/speak Linus \"That's very nice of you, but no thanks! I've had great luck foraging today.$h / 你真好，但是不用了，谢谢！我今天找东西吃的运气很好。$h\"/pause 1000/speak Robin \"Heh... okay.$5 / 嘿……好吧。$5\"/pause 500/faceDirection Robin 3/pause 500/speak Robin \"@? You look like you have something to say... / @？你看起来像有话要说……\"/pause 500/question fork0 \"#I'm just pleased that Linus is doing well...#I'd like to invite Linus to live on the farm with me... / #我只是想说莱纳斯干得不错，这让我很高兴……#我想邀请莱纳斯和我一起住在农场里……\"/pause 100/fork linusWell/faceDirection Robin 2 true/textAboveHead Robin \"Wow! / 哇！\"/showFrame Linus 22/jump Linus/pause 2000/showFrame Linus 0/pause 1000/showFrame Linus 0/faceDirection Robin 2/speak Robin \"That's really generous! What a great idea! I can build a real cozy house for you, Linus.$h / 这么慷慨！真是个好主意！我可以为你建造一间舒适的真房子，莱纳斯。$h\"/move Robin 0 1 1/speak Robin \"You'll finally have running water, heat, a roof over your head... just like the rest of us! Isn't that wonderful, Linus? / 你终于要有自来水、暖气、屋顶了……就像我们其他人一样！是不是很棒，莱纳斯？\"/playMusic spring_day_ambient/pause 1000/showFrame Linus 19/pause 1000/speak Linus \"Er...$s / 呃……$s#$b#Um... No, thanks.$s / 嗯……不用了，谢谢。$s\"/playSound thudStep/showFrame Robin 19/positionOffset Robin 0 -8/pause 40/positionOffset Robin 0 -8/pause 40/positionOffset Robin 0 -8/pause 40/positionOffset Robin 0 -8/pause 40/positionOffset Robin 0 -8/pause 40/positionOffset Robin 0 -8/pause 40/positionOffset Robin 0 -8/pause 40/positionOffset Robin 0 -8/playSound woodWhack/textAboveHead Robin \"Whaa..? / 什么..？\"/pause 1000/emote farmer 8/emote Linus 28/playMusic echos/speak Linus \"I appreciate the kindness... I really do...$s / 我很感激你的善意……真的很……$s#$b#But... I've told you before... I choose to live this way... / 但……我以前告诉过你……我选择以这种方式生活……\"/pause 500/showFrame Linus 0/move Linus 0 1 2/pause 500/speak Linus \"I like to be alone most of the time... I like the quiet sounds... moving with the rhythm of nature... / 大多数时候我喜欢独处……我喜欢天籁之音……随着大自然的节奏起伏……#$b#It's a way of life that I'm comfortable with. I don't ever want to change that. / 这是让我舒适的一种生活方式。我从未想过要改变这一点。\"/showFrame Linus 0/pause 500/move Linus 0 -1 3/faceDirection Linus 3/showFrame Robin 0/pause 1000/speak Robin \"I guess I never thought about it that way...$5 / 我想我从来没有这样想过……$5\"/move Linus 0 1 3/move Linus -2 0 0/faceDirection farmer 2/playMusic spring_day_ambient/speak Linus \"@... I cherish our friendship very much. And I know you do, too.$h / @……我非常珍惜我们的友谊。而且我知道你也是。$h#$b#But... You don't need to try and 'help' me... I know best how to live my own life... okay? / 但……你不需要尝试“帮助”我……我最清楚怎样过自己的生活……好吗？\"/move Linus -2 0 3/faceDirection farmer 3/faceDirection Robin 3/emote farmer 60/speak Linus \"...can you smell that? It's the sweet aroma of ripe berries...$h / ……你闻到了吗？这是成熟浆果的甜香味……$h\"/jump Linus/speed Linus 4/move Linus -4 0 3/move Linus 0 -10 0 true/fade/viewport -2000 -2000/pause 2000/end",
        "linusWell": "pause 100/friendship Linus 250/move Linus 0 1 3/move Linus -2 0 0/faceDirection farmer 2/faceDirection Robin 2/playMusic spring_day_ambient/speak Linus \"Thanks, @. You had me worried, there... I thought you were going to ask me to move on to the farm with you! *wink* / 谢谢，@。你让我担心了，……我以为你会邀请我和你一起搬去农场！*眨眼*#$b#You know, I consider you my closest friend in the valley... you've never tried to 'fix' me... you respect my way of life, even if you don't understand it.$h / 你知道，我将你视作星露谷中最亲密的朋友……你从来没有试图“修正”我……你尊重我的生活方式，即使你无法理解。$h#$b#I really appreciate that. / 我真的很感激。\"/move Linus -2 0 3/faceDirection farmer 3/faceDirection Robin 3/emote farmer 32/speak Linus \"Ah... can you smell that? It's the sweet aroma of ripe berries...$h / 啊……你能闻到吗？这是成熟浆果的甜香味……$h\"/jump Linus/speed Linus 4/move Linus -4 0 3/move Linus 0 -10 0 true/fade/viewport -2000 -2000/pause 500/speak Robin \"Aww.. What a sweetheart...$h / 噢……多么甜心……$h\"/pause 1000/end",
        "384883/f Sebastian 1000/t 1100 1700": "spring_day_ambient/-1000 -1000/farmer 12 27 1 Sebastian 18 26 2/skippable/specificTemporarySprite sebastianGarage/showFrame Sebastian 33/animate Sebastian false true 100 32 32 32 36 32 32 36 36 36 36/positionOffset Sebastian 24 16/viewport 18 25 clamp true/move farmer 5 0 0/playSound clank/move farmer 0 -1 1/pause 100/playSound clank/pause 600/playSound clank/pause 300/playSound clank/pause 800/stopAnimation Sebastian/showFrame Sebastian 35/animate Sebastian false false 100 32 33 34 35/playSound dwoop/pause 500/speak Sebastian \"Oh, hello @.$8 / 哦，你好啊，@。$8\"/pause 800/faceDirection farmer 0/emote farmer 8/pause 400/speak Sebastian \"What, you haven't seen my motorcycle before? Hmmm... I guess I haven't shown it to you.$8 / 什么，你还没有见识过我的摩托车？唔……可能是我没有给你看过。$8\"/pause 900/showFrame Sebastian 32/animate Sebastian false false 100 35 34 33 32/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 1/animate Sebastian false true 200 32 32 32 36 32 32 36 36 36/pause 600/playSound clank/pause 600/playSound clank/pause 300/pause 800/playSound parry/pause 800/playSound clank/playMusic echos/pause 2000/glow 80 70 255 true/pause 1000/speak Sebastian \"Sometimes, after sundown, I make the long ride out of Stardew Valley...$8 / 有时候，在太阳下山以后，我就会骑着它，开出星露谷好远……$8\"/pause 800/speak Sebastian \"There's nothing else like it, blazing along the empty stretch of road toward the faint city glow...$9 / 顺着空旷的公路，向着城里微弱的灯光，一路狂飙，这个感觉无与伦比……$9\"/pause 200/playSound clank/pause 500/playSound clank/pause 200/speak Sebastian \"Once I've saved up enough money, I'm going to head out on my own... to the city and beyond. Just me and my bike.$9 / 等我存够了钱，就要一个人出去闯荡……我要和我的摩托，去比城里还远的地方。就只有我和我的摩托车。$9\"/pause 900/playSound clank/pause 900/stopAnimation Sebastian/playSound Milking/pause 1500/stopGlowing/playMusic spring_day_ambient/speak Sebastian \"There we go, oil's changed.$8 / 好了，油已经换过了。$8\"/pause 1200/showFrame Sebastian 35/animate Sebastian false false 100 32 33 34 35/playSound dwoop/pause 1900/speak Sebastian \"$q -1 null#Hey... Maybe I'll let you ride sometime, if you want.$8 / 嘿……如果你想骑的话，我或许可以让你骑一下。$8^Hey... maybe I'll take you for a ride some day.$8 / 嘿……或许我能找个时间带你兜兜风。$8#$r -1 10 event_garage1#That sounds fun. / 听起来很有趣。#$r -1 -10 event_garage2#No thanks. That sounds stupid. / 不用了，谢谢。我觉得不怎么样。#$r -1 0 event_garage3#I'm scared of motorcycles. / 我很怕摩托车。\"/pause 900/viewport move 1 -1 8000/pause 4000/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/end",
        "26/f Linus 1000/w sunny/t 2000 2400": "nightTime/-1000 -1000/farmer 18 8 1 Linus 29 8 2/skippable/specificTemporarySprite linusCampfire/viewport 29 7 clamp true/move farmer 8 0 1/faceDirection Linus 3/emote Linus 32/speak Linus \"@! Come stand next to the firepit. It feels great. / @！过来烤火哇。感觉很棒呢。\"/pause 400/move farmer 2 0 2/move farmer 0 1 1/move Linus 1 0 2/move Linus 0 1 3/pause 1500/speak Linus \"I was hoping you'd come by sometime. / 我一直希望你能过来找我。\"/pause 500/emote Linus 28/pause 500/faceDirection Linus 2/pause 500/showFrame Linus 19/pause 500/speak Linus \"I wanted to say sorry for mistrusting you at first.$s / 我想为一开始对你的怀疑道歉。$s#$b#Most people don't treat me well, so I've learned to be cautious.$s / 大多数人对我都不好，所以我就变得特别敏感。$s\"/pause 500/showFrame Linus 0/faceDirection Linus 3/speak Linus \"But you've been uncommonly nice to me. You're a unique person.$h / 但你对我真的很好。你是个非常特别的人。$h#$b#...And I consider you a good friend. / 我把你当作好朋友。\"/pause 500/faceDirection Linus 3/emote farmer 32/pause 1000/faceDirection Linus 3/move Linus 0 -1 3/move Linus -1 0 0/speak Linus \"Hey, I want to show you something. Come inside.$h / 嘿，我想给你看件东西。进来。$h\"/move farmer 0 -1 1/move Linus 0 -1 0/playSound grassyStep/warp Linus -10 -10/move farmer 1 0 0/move farmer 0 -1 0/playSound grassyStep/warp farmer -10 -10/playMusic none/pause 1500/playSound fishSlap/pause 500/playSound fishSlap/pause 500/playSound fishSlap/pause 500/playSound fishSlap/pause 800/playSound dirtyHit/pause 1200/playSound slimeHit/pause 300/playSound slimeHit/pause 300/playSound slimeHit/pause 300/playSound slimeHit/pause 600/playSound slimedead/pause 1000/speak Linus \"Ah... there we go. See this? It's a special kind of fish bait that I make. / 瞧。你看见了吗？这是一种我特制的鱼饵。#$b#It's top quality stuff... I'd eat it myself! / 这是最顶级的货色……连我自己都想吃！#$b#Here, I want you to have the recipe. / 给，这是我的配方。\"/pause 500/playSound coin/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 2/warp farmer 29 7/playSound grassyStep/move farmer 0 1 2/pause 1000/showFrame 84/playSound reward/addCraftingRecipe Wild Bait/message \"Learned how to craft 'Wild Bait' / 学会制作“万能鱼饵”\"/pause 900/end",
        "9333219/O Sebastian/f Sebastian 3500/w rainy/t 600 1900": "rain/48 36/farmer 49 31 2 Sebastian 50 36 3/makeInvisible 44 31 5 5/addConversationTopic sebastianFrog 0/skippable/move farmer 0 4 2/faceDirection Sebastian 0/speak Sebastian \"Hey @... Glad you showed up. / 嘿，@……很高兴你来了。\"/emote farmer 8/faceDirection Sebastian 3/speak Sebastian \"There's an injured frog in that bush... I gotta save him! / 有一只受伤的青蛙在灌木丛中……我要去救他！\"/emote farmer 28/faceDirection Sebastian 0/speak Sebastian \"I need your help. Go over to the bush and try to get him to come towards me. I'll wait over here and catch him. / 我需要你的帮助。去那边的灌木丛里试试让他朝我这个方向过来。我会在这里等着抓住他。\"/pause 500/faceDirection Sebastian 3/move farmer -5 0 2/pause 500/showFrame Sebastian 54/playSound grassyStep/pause 500/speak Sebastian \"Okay... you ready? / 好……你准备好了吗？\"/emote farmer 56/textAboveHead Sebastian \"Now! / 就是现在！\"/pause 500/doAction 44 36/pause 1000/doAction 44 36/pause 1000/doAction 44 36/playSound croak/specificTemporarySprite sebastianFrog/pause 10000/playSound coin/showFrame Sebastian 55/jump Sebastian/textAboveHead Sebastian \"Got him! / 抓住他了！\"/move farmer 5 0 2/move farmer 0 1 1/speak Sebastian \"Poor little guy... his foot's all mangled. $s / 可怜的小家伙……他的腿都伤成这样了。$s\"/emote farmer 28/quickQuestion #What should we do with him?#It's our new son...#I don't think he's going to make it#Let's nurse him back to health!(break)speak Sebastian \"I'm gonna take him home for now, and make him comfortable. / 我现在要把他带回家，让他感觉更舒适些。#$b#I guess I'll do some research on how to take care of frogs. Maybe Marnie knows something. / 我想应该去了解一下关于如何照顾青蛙。也许玛妮知道一些。\"(break)speak Sebastian \"Hah... Yeah, I guess so.$h#$b#He's definitely got your nose...$7\"\\faceDirection farmer 2 true\\jump farmer\\showFrame farmer 94\\startJittering(break)emote Sebastian 12\\speak Sebastian \"Well, sorry if I don't take your word for it... I'm gonna give the poor guy a chance.\"(break)speak Sebastian \"We'll do our best. But don't get too attached just yet...\"/pause 300/stopJittering/stopAnimation farmer/faceDirection farmer 1/pause 500/speak Sebastian \"Let's take him home. / 我们带他回家吧。\"/pause 500/playSound croak/pause 2000/end",
        "384882/f Sebastian 2500/t 2000 2400": "nightTime/-1000 -1000/farmer 18 35 0 Sebastian -100 -100 0/skippable/specificTemporarySprite sebastianOnBike/viewport 17 28 clamp true/pause 1000/move farmer 0 -5 0/speak Sebastian \"Hey @. I was just about to head out. / 嘿，@。我正要出发呢。#$b#Hop on...I wanna show you something. / 上来……我想给你看样东西。\"/pause 1000/move farmer 0 -1 0/move farmer 1 0 0 true/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/warp farmer -100 -100/changeToTemporaryMap SebastianRide false/ambientLight 0 0 0/specificTemporarySprite sebastianRide/viewport 15 8 true/pause 8000/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/changeToTemporaryMap SebastianMountain false/ambientLight 0 0 0/warp farmer 15 18/warp Sebastian 16 18/positionOffset farmer 0 16/playMusic spaceMusic/viewport 15 14 clamp true/pause 10000/faceDirection Sebastian 3/speak Sebastian \"That's Zuzu City in the distance... / 远处就是祖祖城……\"/pause 600/faceDirection Sebastian 0/speak Sebastian \"I come here when I want to get away from everything and just... think. / 当我想要逃避一切的时候，就会来到这里，一个人……静静。\"/pause 1000/faceDirection Sebastian 1/pause 600/animate Sebastian false true 110 16 17 18 19 20 21 21 21 21 21 21 21 21 22 23 16 16 16 16 16 16 16 16 16 16 16 16 16 16 16 16 16 16/pause 1000/faceDirection farmer 1/pause 1800/faceDirection farmer 0/pause 800/speak Sebastian \"$q -1 null#So, what do you think? / 那么，你觉得怎么样？#$r -1 0 event_city1#It's beautiful. / 好美啊。#$r -1 10 event_city2#It gives me a strange, sad feeling. / 这让我有一种莫名的伤感。#$r -1 -10 event_city3#Kind of ugly. / 有点儿丑。#$r -1 0 event_city4#You should quit smoking. / 你该戒烟了。\"/stopAnimation Sebastian/pause 600/faceDirection Sebastian 0/pause 3000/speak Sebastian \"The city used to draw me in... but now I'm finding myself happier at home in the valley. / 曾经，我对城里的生活很是着迷……但现在我觉得，在这山谷的老家里，我会更加快乐。\"/pause 500/pause 900/speak Sebastian \"@...?$s / @……？$s#$b#Um... I've never... felt anything like this with another guy before... But you're different.$l / 呃……我从来没对……别人有过这种感觉……但你与众不同。$l^I don't usually bring girls to this place... In fact, you're the only one.$l / 我很少带女孩子来这里……其实，你是唯一一个。$l#$b#You know what I'm trying to say, don't you?$l / 你知道我想说什么，对不对？$l\"/pause 700/faceDirection farmer 1/emote Sebastian 40/pause 800/faceDirection Sebastian 3/pause 2000/showFrame Sebastian 40/pause 600/positionOffset Sebastian -2 0/pause 100/positionOffset Sebastian -2 0/pause 100/positionOffset Sebastian -2 0/pause 100/positionOffset Sebastian -2 0/pause 100/positionOffset Sebastian -2 0/pause 100/positionOffset Sebastian -2 0/pause 100/positionOffset Sebastian -2 0/pause 100/positionOffset Sebastian -2 0/pause 100/positionOffset Sebastian -2 0/pause 100/positionOffset Sebastian -2 0/pause 100/positionOffset Sebastian -2 0/pause 100/positionOffset Sebastian -2 0/pause 100/showFrame 101/pause 4000/viewport move 1 -1 6000/pause 6000/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/changeLocation Mountain/pause 4000/end position 18 26",
        "2/f Abigail 1000/w rainy/t 1200 1900/z winter": "AbigailFlute/-1000 -1000/farmer 34 32 1 Abigail 47 31 2/skippable/ambientLight 160 140 10/specificTemporarySprite abbyAtLake/animate Abigail false true 612 16 17 18 19/viewport 46 31 clamp true/pause 17900/move farmer 13 0 0/stopMusic/playMusic rain/pause 500/stopAnimation Abigail/faceDirection Abigail 2/emote Abigail 16/speak Abigail \"$q 32 null#@! Why are you out here in the rain?$7 / @！你怎么站在雨里啊？$7#$r 32 0 Event_Rain_1#Just doing some work / 我在干活儿#$r 32 50 Event_Rain_2#Enjoying the weather / 我在享受这种天气#$r 32 10 Event_Rain_3#I could ask you the same question / 我还想问你呢\"/faceDirection Abigail 1/pause 1250/speak Abigail \"...I came here to spend some time alone.$8 / 我想一个人在这儿静静。$8\"/pause 1000/faceDirection farmer 1/pause 1600/faceDirection Abigail 2/speak Abigail \"But I don't mind your company! / 你陪我也好！\"/pause 500/emote Abigail 40/speak Abigail \"You're getting soaked... come stand under the tree. / 你都淋透了……来，站到树底下。\"/move farmer -1 0 0/move farmer 0 -1 2/faceDirection Abigail 1/pause 3000/speak Abigail \"It's impossible to describe this feeling... watching the curtains of rain whisper above a silent lake.$8 / 看着雨帘在寂静的湖面上飘荡……这种感觉难以形容。$8\"/pause 650/faceDirection farmer 1/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 600/playSound dwop/showFrame 98/pause 500/faceDirection Abigail 3/emote Abigail 16/pause 800/speak Abigail \"Hey! A mini-harp!$h / 嘿！迷你竖琴！$h#$b#You're full of surprises, @. I'm impressed. / 你身上到处充满惊喜，@。我很惊讶。\"/faceDirection farmer 1/pause 900/emote farmer 56/faceDirection Abigail 3/pause 700/faceDirection Abigail 2/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 500/showFrame Abigail 16/pause 500/showFrame 98/pause 2000/playMusic AbigailFluteDuet/pause 1250/animate Abigail false true 612 16 17 18 19/animate farmer false true 308 99 98 98 99 100 100/pause 10000/viewport move 1 0 18000/pause 20000/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 2000/end",
        "5183338/e 3917666/O Maru/w sunny/t 2200 2500": "nightTime/-1000 -1000/farmer 23 29 3 Maru 14 29 3/skippable/changeToTemporaryMap NightSceneMaruMap2 false/bgColor 0 0 0/ambientLight 0 0 0/viewport 14 25 true clamp/pause 1000/move farmer -8 0 3/faceDirection Maru 1/pause 800/showFrame Maru 32/pause 700/showFrame Maru 4/speak Maru \"Hey, @. You made it just in time... The comet's about to appear. / 嘿，@。你来得正好……彗星就要出现了。\"/pause 500/faceDirection Maru 2/pause 1000/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 1000/speak Maru \"Beautiful night, isn't it? / 这夜空真美丽，是不是？\"/pause 2000/faceDirection Maru 1/faceDirection farmer 3/pause 1000/speak Maru \"Remember the first time we did this? It was a while ago... / 还记得我们第一次来观星吗？已经是挺久以前了……\"/faceDirection Maru 2/speak Maru \"I almost revealed my true feelings on that night... but I was afraid you'd reject me. / 那天晚上我差点就把真正的心意说出来了……但我担心你会拒绝我。\"/faceDirection Maru 1/speak Maru \"Who knew we'd be married so soon after!$h / 谁知道之后我们这么快就结婚了！$h\"/pause 500/emote farmer 20/pause 500/jump Maru/pause 400/speak Maru \"Oh! It's time... / 哦！要来了……\"/faceDirection Maru 3/faceDirection farmer 3 true/showFrame Maru 28/emote Maru 40/pause 1000/textAboveHead Maru \"Wow! / 哇哦！\"/pause 3000/showFrame Maru 12/move Maru 0 1 0/speak Maru \"Take a look! / 快看！\"/pause 500/move farmer -1 0 3/pause 1000/animate farmer true true 100 35/pause 1000/fade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 1000/playMusic spaceMusic/warp Maru 15 29/faceDirection Maru 3/cutscene marucomet/pause 1000/viewport 14 25 true clamp/pause 3000/stopAnimation farmer/pause 1000/faceDirection farmer 1/pause 500/speak Maru \"After seeing a comet, it's customary to make a wish... / 看到彗星之后，按照惯例该许个愿……\"/pause 500/quickQuestion What will you wish for?#A new baby#For us to grow old together#More money(break)jump Maru\\pause 500\\speak Maru \"Oh! We can certainly try...$l / 哦！我们当然可以去努力一下……$l\"\\emote Maru 20(break)emote Maru 20\\speak Maru \"That's... really sweet!$l#$b#I have the same wish.$l\"(break)speak Maru \"Money? Oh...$s#$b#Well I guess that would be practical...$8\"\\emote Maru 28\\speak Maru \"My wish is a little more romantic...\"/pause 2000/animate Maru false true 100 28/animate farmer false true 100 101/positionOffset farmer 16 0/specificTemporarySprite heart 15 29/pause 2000/specificTemporarySprite maruTelescope/viewport move 0 -1 13000/pause 16000/fade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 3000/end newDay",
        "8357109/w sunny/t 600 1900/n linusTrashCleanup": "spring_day_ambient/-1000 -1000/farmer -100 -100 2 Linus 63 21 2/skippable/hideShadow Linus true/showFrame Linus 24/specificTemporarySprite staticSprite LooseSprites\\\\Cursors2 129 241 14 15 60 20/viewport 63 21 true/pause 5000/speak Linus \"Ahhh... that feels good.$4 / 啊……感觉真不错。$4\"/pause 1000/speak Linus \"The water's never been cleaner.$4 / 这里的水从来都不会变得更干净。$4\"/pause 2000/speak Linus \"...And the same goes for me! Hehehe.$5 / ……我也不会变得更干净！嘿嘿嘿。$5\"/pause 3000/end",
        "8959199/w sunny/t 600 1900/e 6497428/f Leo 2250/F": "sad_kid/-1000 -1000/farmer -100 -100 2 Linus 30 9 3 Leo 28 9 1 Penny -100 -100 2 Jas -100 -100 3 Vincent -100 -100 1/skippable/specificTemporarySprite LeoLinusCooking/animate Linus true true 500 20 21/viewport 26 9 clamp true/viewport move 1 0 10000/pause 1000/textAboveHead Leo \"It's ready! / 准备好了！\"/pause 4000/textAboveHead Linus \"Not yet... / 还不行……\"/pause 1500/emote Leo 28 true/pause 500/fade/viewport -1000 -1000/changeLocation ArchaeologyHouse/warp Penny 18 9/warp Linus -100 -100/showFrame Penny 18/warp Jas 19 10/showFrame Jas 22/warp Vincent 16 10/showFrame Vincent 24/warp Leo 18 12/showFrame Leo 24/pause 500/viewport 13 10 clamp true/viewport move 1 0 8000/pause 2000/textAboveHead Penny \"Good answer, Leo! / 好回答，雷欧！\"/pause 1000/emote Leo 20 true/pause 2000/fade/viewport -1000 -1000/warp Penny -100 -100/warp Jas -100 -100/warp Jas -100 -100/changeLocation Beach/warp Leo 42 36/showFrame Leo 0/addTemporaryActor Willy 16 64 43 38 2/animate Willy false true 500 8 9 10 11/viewport 36 36 clamp true/viewport move 1 0 8000/pause 1000/emote Leo 40/pause 2000/shake Willy 3000/showFrame Leo 16/jump Leo/playSound waterSlosh/animate Willy false true 200 17 18/pause 500/specificTemporarySprite LeoWillyFishing/playSound dropItemInWater/textAboveHead Willy \"Got one, lad! / 拿到一个了，哥们！\"/pause 500/playSound waterSlosh/pause 500/playSound waterSlosh/pause 500/fade/viewport -1000 -1000/changeLocation Town/warp Vincent -100 -100/warp Willy -100 -100/warp Jas 18 16/animate Jas false true 80 16 17 18 19/warp Leo 25 15/faceDirection Leo 3/viewport 18 16 clamp true/viewport move 1 0 9000/pause 3000/doAction 24 16/pause 500/doAction 24 16/stopAnimation Jas/faceDirection Jas 1/emote Jas 8/doAction 24 16/showFrame Leo 16/shake Leo 3000/jump Leo/positionOffset Leo 4 0/pause 100/positionOffset Leo 4 0/pause 100/positionOffset Leo 4 0/pause 100/speed Leo 4/emote Jas 16 true/advancedMove Leo false 3 0 0 4 7 0/pause 2000/fade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 600/changeLocation LeoTreeHouse/pause 500/warp Vincent -100 -100/warp Jas -100 -100/viewport 3 3 true/pause 4000/stopAnimation Leo/faceDirection Leo 0/warp Leo 3 8/playSound doorClose/move Leo 0 -3 0/move Leo -1 0 3/doAction 1 5/pause 500/speak Leo \"Haha! ...That was a great day!$h / 哈哈！……今天真是美好的一天！$h\"/pause 1000/faceDirection Leo 2/pause 1000/showFrame Leo 18/pause 1000/speak Leo \"You know... I still miss my family back on the island...$s / 你知道的……我仍在想念我在岛上的家人……$s\"/pause 400/showFrame Leo 0/speak Leo \"But mostly, I feel happy about the memories, not sad. / 但大多数时候，我对那些回忆感到高兴，而不是悲伤。\"/pause 400/faceDirection Leo 3/speak Leo \"...and I really feel like I belong here!$h / ……并且我真的认为自己属于这里！$h\"/pause 500/doAction 1 5/pause 500/doAction 1 5/pause 1000/move Leo 0 -3 0/pause 2000/speak Leo \"It's a beautiful world, friends... / 这是个美丽的世界，朋友……\"/pause 600/faceDirection Leo 1 true/pause 140/faceDirection Leo 2/pause 800/speak Leo \"...and I'm glad to be part of it!$h / ……我很高兴能成为美丽世界的一部分！$h\"/pause 1000/doAction 1 5/pause 1000/fade/viewport -2000 -2000/pause 1500/end",
        "BadAnswer": "speak Maru \"$q 18982 null#You must have a good reason for saying that...$a / 你会那么说，肯定有原因……$a#$r 18982 50 event_robot_explain1#MarILDA's just a piece of machinery designed to act human. / 玛丽尔达就是一台设计用来模仿人类的机器。#$r 18982 50 event_robot_explain2#I was just kidding. MarILDA deserves her freedom. / 我刚才是在开玩笑。玛丽尔达应该享有自由的权力。#$r 18982 -50 event_robot_explain3#I would've put her to work on the farm. / 我会让她去农场里工作。\"/faceDirection Maru 1/emote Maru 12/pause 300/faceDirection Maru 3/speak Maru \"Well, I should go. Thanks for sticking with me today, @.$8 / 好啦，我该走了。感谢你今天陪我，@。$8\"/globalFade/viewport -3000 -3000/changeLocation ScienceHouse/end"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Events/QiNutRoom",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "10040609": "clubloop/7 4/farmer 7 8 0 MrQi 7 4 0/skippable/move farmer 0 -2 0/pause 3000/speak MrQi \"Well, well, well... Look who's made it to my secret walnut room. / 哦哟哟……看看是谁找到了我的隐藏核桃房间。\"/pause 1000/faceDirection MrQi 1 true/pause 100/faceDirection MrQi 2/pause 1000/speak MrQi \"I'm truly impressed. / 实在了不起。#$b#Even though you only needed a fraction of the walnuts to gain full access to the island, you decided to push yourself further. / 尽管你只需要一小部分核桃就可以在岛上自由地通行，但是你还是更进了一步。#$b#Your desire to enter this secret door was so strong, that you went above and beyond to get inside. / 你进入这扇隐藏门的渴望极为强烈，所以付出超过常人的努力到达了这里。#$b#That drive is what sets you apart, kid. You've got a very special energy. / 这份热忱让你出类拔萃，孩子。你拥有特别的能量。\"/pause 1000/faceDirection MrQi 3 true/pause 100/faceDirection MrQi 0/pause 500/speak MrQi \"That being said... / 话虽如此……#$b#You weren't under the impression that the challenge ended here, were you? / 你不会以为挑战就到此为止了吧？#$b#No... Hah. Hah. Hah... In fact, the challenge has just begun. / 并没有……哈、哈、哈……事实上，挑战才刚刚开始。\"/faceDirection MrQi 3 true/pause 40/faceDirection MrQi 2/pause 1000/faceDirection MrQi 3/speak MrQi \"On your left, you'll find a board with some very interesting opportunities. / 在你的左手边有一块看板，上面有一些很有趣的机遇。#$b#These challenges, which I've designed just for you, will push you to your very limit. / 这些挑战是我专门为你设计的，它们会让你挑战极限。\"/faceDirection MrQi 2/speak MrQi \"However, if you can successfully conquer my challenges, you'll earn an exclusive currency... I call them 'Qi Gems' / 不过，如果能攻克我的挑战，你会获得一种独特的货币……我称之为“齐钻”。\"/pause 400/speak MrQi \"Just don't put 'em in your mouth, kid... They're highly radioactive. Heh. heh. heh... / 记得别把它们放到嘴里，孩子……它们放射性很强。呵、呵、呵……\"/emote farmer 28/pause 500/faceDirection MrQi 1/speak MrQi \"You can use the machine on your right to trade these Qi Gems for rare and powerful rewards. / 你可以在右手边的机器上用齐钻兑换一些罕见而且强大的奖励。\"/pause 1000/faceDirection MrQi 2/speak MrQi \"Sounds interesting, doesn't it? / 听起来是不是很有趣？#$b#Yes... I have a feeling someone like you will enjoy this, very much... / 是啊……我觉得像你这样的人会觉得很有意思，很有意思……\"/pause 400/faceDirection MrQi 1 true/pause 50/faceDirection MrQi 0/pause 500/speak MrQi \"Now, if you'll excuse me... I have important business to attend to. / 好了，我还有更重要的事情要做……告辞。\"/pause 2000/end"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Events/Railroad",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "529952/C": "WizardSong/54 36/Wizard 54 36 0 farmer 50 40 1/addQuest 28/skippable/move farmer 1 0 0/move farmer 0 -4 1/faceDirection Wizard 3 true/move farmer 1 0 1/pause 800/faceDirection Wizard 0/pause 600/emote Wizard 40/pause 500/speak Wizard \"Ah... @. I've been waiting for you. / 呃…@。我在等你。\"/pause 800/faceDirection Wizard 3/pause 400/faceDirection Wizard 0/pause 400/speak Wizard \"Have I ever told you I used to be married? / 我有告诉过你我过去曾结过婚吗？\"/pause 800/faceDirection Wizard 3 true/pause 50/faceDirection Wizard 2/pause 800/showFrame Wizard 18/pause 800/speak Wizard \"Strange, I know... for a man like me. But it's true. / 作为一个像我这样的男人，我知道这很奇怪…但这是事实。\"/pause 500/showFrame Wizard 0/pause 800/faceDirection Wizard 3/speak Wizard \"My wife and I were together for many years, until... until I made a mistake that drove her away. / 我和我前妻一起生活了很多年，直…直到我犯了一个错误导致她离开了。\"/pause 400/faceDirection Wizard 0/speak Wizard \"Her anger and envy were so intense that she turned green and began flying around the countryside, cursing everything in her path... / 她的愤怒和嫉妒是如此强烈，以至于她全身变成绿色，开始在乡村周围飞行，诅咒着她在路上遭遇的一切……\"/pause 1000/speak Wizard \"When I found out, I sealed this passage to her home... fearing that an innocent villager might fall prey to her dark magic. / 当我发现时，我把这条通道封锁到她的家里…………担心一个无辜的村民可能会被她的黑魔法所掠夺。\"/move Wizard -1 0 3/speak Wizard \"But now, it must be unsealed... for when we separated, she took my magic ink! / 但现在，肯定被解封了…我们分开的时候，她拿走了我的魔法药水！#$b#I need that magic ink back!$h / 我需要拿回那药水！$h#$b#I would do this myself, but I... I can't see her again. That's why I need your help. / 我本是通过自己来完成的，但我…我再也不能看见她。所以我才需要你的帮忙。\"/move Wizard 1 0 0/speak Wizard \"In order to unseal this passage, you'll need a dark talisman. Talk to Krobus, in the sewer... he should know where to find one. / 为了解封这条通道，你需要一个黑暗护符。与下水道的科罗布斯交谈，他应该知道在哪能得到。\"/pause 500/faceDirection Wizard 3/speak Wizard \"I'm counting on you... if you can retrieve my magic ink I promise I'll make it worth your while... Now go! / 我全指望你了…如果你能取回我的魔法药水我承诺我将会给你值得的东西…现在赶紧出发吧！\"/pause 500/faceDirection Wizard 2/pause 500/showFrame Wizard 16/pause 500/playSound wand/warp Wizard -3000 -3000/specificTemporarySprite wizardWarp2/faceDirection farmer 2 true/showFrame farmer 94/pause 3000/showFrame farmer 0/specificTemporarySprite witchFlyby/pause 4000/end",
        "afraid": "pause 500/speak Harvey \"I am... yeah.$s / 是……没错。$s#$b#But I'm determined to not let that stop me from doing what I want... and experiencing this with you.$l / 但我已经下定决心，不能让它阻碍我的梦想……还有陪在你身边的机会。$l#$b#I'll try not to get scared. / 我要试着克服恐惧。\"/pause 400/move farmer 0 1 1/faceDirection Harvey 1/move farmer 3 0 0/move farmer 0 -1 0/jump farmer 14/move farmer 0 -1 2/move Harvey 0 1 1/move Harvey 3 0 0/move Harvey 0 -1 0/jump Harvey 14/move Harvey 0 -1 2/pause 1000/showFrame Harvey 29/pause 300/playSound openBox/pause 300/showFrame Harvey 0/pause 400/playSound furnace/cutscene balloonDepart/playMusic none/viewport move 0 -1 6000/pause 2000/showFrame Harvey 30/jump Harvey 5/shake Harvey 7000/pause 7000/globalFade/viewport -2000 -2000/playMusic 50s/pause 2000/cutscene clearTempSprites/changeToTemporaryMap HarveyBalloon/cutscene balloonChangeMap/viewport -2000 -2000/warp farmer 22 36/warp Harvey 22 36/positionOffset farmer 24 570/positionOffset Harvey 96 554/positionOffset farmer -8 -8/positionOffset Harvey -24 -8/showFrame Harvey 32/pause 1000/shake Harvey 19000/viewport 23 39 clamp true/viewport move 0 -1 17000/pause 18000/faceDirection farmer 1/showFrame Harvey 33/pause 1000/jump Harvey/showFrame Harvey 30/pause 800/showFrame Harvey 12/animate Harvey false true 100 12 13 14 15/positionOffset Harvey -4 2/pause 30/positionOffset Harvey -4 2/pause 30/positionOffset Harvey -4 2/pause 30/positionOffset Harvey -4 2/pause 30/positionOffset Harvey -4 2/pause 30/positionOffset Harvey -4 2/pause 30/positionOffset Harvey -4 2/pause 30/positionOffset Harvey -4 2/pause 30/stopAnimation Harvey/showFrame Harvey 31/positionOffset Harvey -4 0/playSound fishSlap/eyes 1 -2000/pause 2000/speak Harvey \"We... We're up so high... *gulp*$8 / 好……好高啊……*咽口水*$8\"/shake Harvey 2000/pause 800/speak Harvey \"I wanted to impress you with this... but look at me. I'm a trembling coward.$7 / 我本想用这个来打动你……但被你看到我吓成这个样子。我真是个胆小鬼。$7\"/emote Harvey 28/pause 500/speak Harvey \"Well, you've got more than enough courage to make up for me, @... that's... that's part of why I like you.$11 / 嗯，你的勇气十足，这正能弥补我的不足，@……那……那就是我喜欢你的原因之一。$11\"/pause 1000/speak Harvey \"Okay, I'm going to open my eyes and look down... don't let go of my hand.$4 / 好的，我正准备睁开眼睛并往下看……不要放开我的手。$4\"/pause 800/positionOffset Harvey 4 -2/pause 30/positionOffset Harvey 4 -2/pause 30/positionOffset Harvey 4 -2/pause 30/positionOffset Harvey 4 -2/pause 30/positionOffset Harvey 4 0/pause 30/positionOffset Harvey 4 0/pause 30/faceDirection farmer 2/showFrame Harvey 0/pause 500/showFrame Harvey 33/pause 500/shake Harvey 4000/pause 500/showFrame Harvey 30/pause 2000/showFrame Harvey 33/pause 3500/speak Harvey \"I... I think I can do it now.$8 / 我……现在应该可以了。$8\"/specificTemporarySprite balloonBirds/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 3000/faceDirection Harvey 1/faceDirection farmer 1/emote farmer 16 true/emote Harvey 16/pause 4000/faceDirection farmer 0/faceDirection Harvey 2/pause 10000/speak Harvey \"Hey, this is incredible! I think I can see Mayor Lewis standing in the town square!$h / 嘿，这太不可思议了！我能看到在广场上的镇长刘易斯！$h\"/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 3000/speak Harvey \"Oh dear... our time's almost up.$s / 天哪……时间快到了。$s\"/pause 400/faceDirection Harvey 3/faceDirection farmer 1/playMusic none/pause 500/speak Harvey \"Um... @? We've known each other for a while now and... I... er...$11 / 呃……@？我们已经认识一段时间了……我，呃……$11\"/playMusic musicboxsong/pause 400/faceDirection Harvey 2/pause 500/faceDirection Harvey 3/speak Harvey \"...$11 / ……$11\"/specificTemporarySprite balloonBirds 2/pause 1000/showFrame Harvey 31/pause 500/showFrame 101/positionOffset Harvey -1 0/pause 30/positionOffset Harvey -1 -2/pause 30/positionOffset Harvey -1 -2/pause 30/positionOffset Harvey -1 0/pause 30/positionOffset Harvey -1 0/pause 30/positionOffset Harvey -1 0/pause 30/positionOffset Harvey -1 0/pause 30/positionOffset Harvey -1 0/pause 30/pause 5000/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 5000/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 2000/speak Harvey \"Whoops... Our time was up half an hour ago. We'd better touch down.$l / 噢不……我们只剩下半小时了。我们最好赶紧落地。$l\"/pause 2000/end dialogue Harvey \"I haven't had such a wonderful day for as long as I can remember.$l\"",
        "528052/f Harvey 2500/t 900 1700/n harveyBalloon": "playful/26 38/Harvey 24 41 0 farmer 24 50 0/skippable/move farmer 0 -8 0/faceDirection Harvey 2/speak Harvey \"There you are... just in time!$l / 你来得正好！$l\"/faceDirection Harvey 0/jump Harvey/pause 800/speak Harvey \"Look, here it comes!$8 / 瞧，它来了！$8\"/emote farmer 8/move Harvey -1 0 1/move farmer -2 0 0/move farmer 0 -1 1/addTemporaryActor Marcello 16 32 25 19 2 true/positionOffset Marcello 36 558/animate Marcello false true 400 16 17/specificTemporarySprite marcelloLand/null/pause 1000/stopAnimation Marcello/pause 500/message \"Marcello's Balloon Rentals at your service! / 马尔赛罗热气球租赁行为您服务！\"/pause 1000/positionOffset Marcello -4 0/pause 20/positionOffset Marcello -4 0/pause 20/positionOffset Marcello -4 0/pause 20/positionOffset Marcello -4 0/pause 20/positionOffset Marcello -4 0/pause 20/positionOffset Marcello -4 0/pause 20/positionOffset Marcello -4 0/pause 20/positionOffset Marcello -4 0/pause 20/positionOffset Marcello -4 0/pause 20/jump Marcello 12/move Marcello 0 3 3/move Marcello -2 0 0/faceDirection Harvey 2/faceDirection farmer 2/message \"Marcello: It's all yours for two hours. / 马尔赛罗：在接下来的两个小时里，任君使用。\"/faceDirection Marcello 3/faceDirection Marcello 2/message \"Marcello: Now... I was told there's a saloon somewhere around here? / 马尔赛罗：那个……我听说这附近有个酒吧？\"/move Marcello 0 9 1/warp Marcello -100 -100/faceDirection farmer 1/faceDirection Harvey 3/pause 500/speak Harvey \"I saw an ad in the paper for these balloon rides and I knew I had to surprise you with one. / 我在报纸上看到一条广告，说有热气球可以坐，我就知道可以给你一个惊喜。\"/pause 800/question fork1 \"#This looks fun! Let's ride!#...But aren't you afraid of heights? / #好有趣的样子啊！我们坐坐吧！#但你不是怕高吗？\"/fork afraid/pause 500/speak Harvey \"Okay... you first.$l / 好吧……你先请。$l\"/pause 400/move farmer 0 1 1/faceDirection Harvey 1/move farmer 3 0 0/move farmer 0 -1 0/jump farmer 14/move farmer 0 -1 2/move Harvey 0 1 1/move Harvey 3 0 0/move Harvey 0 -1 0/jump Harvey 14/move Harvey 0 -1 2/pause 1000/showFrame Harvey 29/pause 300/playSound openBox/pause 300/showFrame Harvey 0/pause 400/playSound furnace/playMusic none/cutscene balloonDepart/viewport move 0 -1 6000/pause 2000/showFrame Harvey 30/jump Harvey 5/shake Harvey 7000/pause 7000/globalFade/viewport -2000 -2000/playMusic 50s/pause 2000/cutscene clearTempSprites/changeToTemporaryMap HarveyBalloon/cutscene balloonChangeMap/viewport -2000 -2000/warp farmer 22 36/warp Harvey 22 36/positionOffset farmer 24 570/positionOffset Harvey 96 554/positionOffset farmer -8 -8/positionOffset Harvey -24 -8/showFrame Harvey 32/pause 1000/shake Harvey 19000/viewport 23 39 clamp true/viewport move 0 -1 17000/pause 18000/faceDirection farmer 1/showFrame Harvey 33/pause 1000/jump Harvey/showFrame Harvey 30/pause 800/showFrame Harvey 12/animate Harvey false true 100 12 13 14 15/positionOffset Harvey -4 2/pause 30/positionOffset Harvey -4 2/pause 30/positionOffset Harvey -4 2/pause 30/positionOffset Harvey -4 2/pause 30/positionOffset Harvey -4 2/pause 30/positionOffset Harvey -4 2/pause 30/positionOffset Harvey -4 2/pause 30/positionOffset Harvey -4 2/pause 30/stopAnimation Harvey/showFrame Harvey 31/positionOffset Harvey -4 0/playSound fishSlap/eyes 1 -2000/pause 2000/speak Harvey \"We... We're up so high... *gulp*$8 / 好……好高啊……*咽口水*$8\"/shake Harvey 2000/pause 800/speak Harvey \"I wanted to impress you with this... but look at me. I'm a trembling coward.$7 / 我本想用这个来打动你……但被你看到我吓成这个样子。我真是个胆小鬼。$7\"/emote Harvey 28/pause 500/speak Harvey \"Well, you've got more than enough courage to make up for me, @... that's... that's part of why I like you.$11 / 嗯，你的勇气十足，这正能弥补我的不足，@……那……那就是我喜欢你的原因之一。$11\"/pause 1000/speak Harvey \"Okay, I'm going to open my eyes and look down... don't let go of my hand.$4 / 好的，我正准备睁开眼睛并往下看……不要放开我的手。$4\"/pause 800/positionOffset Harvey 4 -2/pause 30/positionOffset Harvey 4 -2/pause 30/positionOffset Harvey 4 -2/pause 30/positionOffset Harvey 4 -2/pause 30/positionOffset Harvey 4 0/pause 30/positionOffset Harvey 4 0/pause 30/faceDirection farmer 2/showFrame Harvey 0/pause 500/showFrame Harvey 33/pause 500/shake Harvey 4000/pause 500/showFrame Harvey 30/pause 2000/showFrame Harvey 33/pause 3500/speak Harvey \"I... I think I can do it now.$8 / 我……现在应该可以了。$8\"/specificTemporarySprite balloonBirds/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 3000/faceDirection Harvey 1/faceDirection farmer 1/emote farmer 16 true/emote Harvey 16/pause 4000/faceDirection farmer 0/faceDirection Harvey 2/pause 10000/speak Harvey \"Hey, this is incredible! I think I can see Mayor Lewis standing in the town square!$h / 嘿，这太不可思议了！我能看到在广场上的镇长刘易斯！$h\"/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 3000/speak Harvey \"Oh dear... our time's almost up.$s / 天哪……时间快到了。$s\"/pause 400/faceDirection Harvey 3/faceDirection farmer 1/playMusic none/pause 500/speak Harvey \"Um... @? We've known each other for a while now and... I... er...$11 / 呃……@？我们已经认识一段时间了……我，呃……$11\"/playMusic musicboxsong/pause 400/faceDirection Harvey 2/pause 500/faceDirection Harvey 3/speak Harvey \"...$11 / ……$11\"/specificTemporarySprite balloonBirds 2/pause 1000/showFrame Harvey 31/pause 500/showFrame 101/positionOffset Harvey -1 0/pause 30/positionOffset Harvey -1 -2/pause 30/positionOffset Harvey -1 -2/pause 30/positionOffset Harvey -1 0/pause 30/positionOffset Harvey -1 0/pause 30/positionOffset Harvey -1 0/pause 30/positionOffset Harvey -1 0/pause 30/positionOffset Harvey -1 0/pause 30/pause 5000/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 2000/speak Harvey \"Whoops... Our time was up half an hour ago. We'd better touch down.$l / 噢不……我们只剩下半小时了。我们最好赶紧落地。$l\"/pause 2000/end dialogue Harvey \"I haven't had such a wonderful day for as long as I can remember.$l\""
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Events/Saloon",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "195099/f Shane 2500/f Sebastian 2500/f Sam 2500/f Harvey 2500/f Alex 2500/f Elliott 2500/o Abigail/o Penny/o Leah/o Emily/o Maru/o Haley/o Shane/o Harvey/o Sebastian/o Sam/o Elliott/o Alex/e 911526/e 528052/e 9581348/e 43/e 384882/e 233104/i 446/k 195013": "playful/-1000 -1000/farmer 27 19 1 Sam 36 20 1 Sebastian 37 19 2 Harvey 39 19 2 Shane 40 17 2 Elliott 41 19 2 Alex 42 20 3/animate Shane false true 200 20 20 20 20 20 20 20 20 20 20 21 22 23 24 24 24 24 23 22 21 20 20 20 20/pause 1000/message \"For some reason, you decide to place your hand in your pocket... / 出于某些原因，你决定把手放到口袋里……\"/pause 500/message \"You touch the rabbit's foot, and feel a sense of relief... / 你摸着兔子的脚，感觉如释重负……\"/move farmer 5 0 1 true/viewport 37 19 true/move false/pause 500/faceDirection Sam 3 true/faceDirection Elliott 3 true/faceDirection Harvey 3 true/faceDirection Alex 3 true/faceDirection Shane 3 true/faceDirection Sebastian 3 true/textAboveHead Sam \"Hey! / 嘿！\"/textAboveHead Alex \"What's up? / 最近好吗？\"/textAboveHead Shane \"Oh, hey / 哦，你好\"/pause 2000/move farmer 3 0 1/emote farmer 32/pause 500/speak Harvey \"You showed up just in time for the first ever Pelican Town 8-ball tournament! / 你来得正是时候，刚好赶上鹈鹕镇第一届八球锦标赛！\"/pause 500/speak Elliott \"Don't worry, I've never played before, either.$h / 别担心，我以前也没玩过。$h\"/pause 500/speak Shane \"It's easy, you just gotta put some mustard on the cue ball...$h / 很简单的，你只管猛击母球就对了……$h\"/pause 500/fade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 1500/message \"You played a round of pool with the boys. / 你和男孩们玩了一局桌球。\"/pause 1000/message \"Sebastian won, of course... but it was still a lot of fun! / 毫无悬念，塞巴斯蒂安赢了……不过还是很有趣！\"/pause 500/end",
        "40/f Elliott 1000/p Gus/t 1500 2200": "playful/11 20/farmer 14 24 0 Elliott -30 -30 0 Clint 18 22 2 Marnie 9 22 3 Pam 7 18 1 Lewis 8 22 1 Pierre 4 22 2 Demetrius 3 23 1 Gus 14 18 2 Emily 16 18 3/skippable/move farmer 0 -3 3/faceDirection Pierre 1 true/move farmer -3 0 0/faceDirection Pierre 2 true/move farmer 0 -1 0/faceDirection Marnie 0 true/faceDirection Gus 3/speak Gus \"Hi. I'll take your order in a few moments. / 嗨，我马上就来给您点单。\"/faceDirection Gus 2/move Emily 2 0 1/faceDirection Marnie 3 true/pause 800/move Emily -2 0 0/pause 1000/faceDirection Clint 3 true/move Emily 2 0 1/warp Elliott 14 24/playSound doorClose/pause 500/move Elliott 0 -3 3/faceDirection farmer 2 true/move Elliott -2 0 0/move Elliott 0 -1 0/faceDirection farmer 1/faceDirection Elliott 3/speak Elliott \"Hello, @! What a pleasant surprise! / 您好，@!真是巧啊！#$b#I was just stopping in to relax after an eight hour writing session.$h / 我刚写了八个小时的书，想来这里休息一下。$h\"/pause 400/faceDirection Elliott 1/speak Elliott \"Bartender! Two of your finest ales, please! / 酒保！请来两杯最好的麦芽酒！^Bartender! Fetch me your finest ale. And bring some wine for the lady! / 酒保！我要你们最好的麦芽酒。再给这位女士来杯葡萄酒！\"/faceDirection Gus 3/faceDirection farmer 0/speak Gus \"...$u / ……$u\"/move Gus 3 0 0/move Gus 0 -1 0/faceDirection Emily 2/playSound openBox/pause 400/playSound Milking/move Pam -6 0 0/move Gus 0 1 3/move Gus -5 0 2/faceDirection Elliott 0/pause 500/speak Gus \"There you go, sir.$u / 给您，先生。$u\"/pause 500/faceDirection Elliott 3/faceDirection farmer 1/speak Elliott \"$q 28376 null#Wait. I propose a toast! To... / 等等。让我们举杯庆祝一下！为了……#$r 28376 25 event_toast4#To Pelican Town! / 鹈鹕镇！#$r 28376 50 event_toast2#To our friendship! / 我们的友谊！#$r 28376 -10 event_toast1#To my good health! / 我们的健康！#$r 28376 -50 event_toast3#To your doom! / 你的命运！\"/faceDirection Elliott 2/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 900/showFrame Elliott 16/animate Elliott false false 120 16 17 18 19 19 18 18 19 19 18 18 19 19 18 18 19 19 18 18 17 16/pause 500/farmerEat 346/pause 900/pause 1100/stopAnimation farmer/faceDirection farmer 1/speak Elliott \"*Hic*... Strong stuff...$h / *打嗝*……劲儿好大啊……$h\"/pause 800/animate Elliott false false 400 20 21 22 21 20 21 22 21 20 21 22 21 20 21 22 21 16/pause 1000/faceDirection farmer 1/pause 800/faceDirection farmer 2/animate farmer false true 100 102 103/pause 1000/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 600/stopAnimation farmer/end warpOut",
        "choseToExplain": "pause 100/textAboveHead Shane \"I doubt it... / 我深表怀疑……\"/pause 500/resetVariable/question fork2 \"#You were all too pushy with me! You made it difficult to say 'no'!#Pierre pressured me! He wanted to sell more bouquets!#(Start crying) / #你们所有人都在逼我！让我说不出“不”！#皮埃尔向我施压！他想卖出更多花束！#（开始哭）\"/pause 100/fork crying/textAboveHead Sam \"Liar! / 骗子！\"/textAboveHead Alex \"Yeah, right! / 对，没错！\"/speak Elliott \"Don't blame others for your mistakes! You're just losing more respect with us...$a / 不要把自己的错误归咎在别人身上！你只会继续失去我们的尊重……$a\"/pause 1000/faceDirection Sam 2/playMusic none/speak Sam \"...I think we've come to a decision... isn't that right, boys?$u / ……我想我们已经决定了……对吗，男孩们？$u\"/pause 500/speak Harvey \"...yes.$s / ……是的。$s\"/speak Sebastian \"Absolutely.$a / 当然。$a\"/faceDirection Sam 3/pause 1000/jump Sam/jump Sebastian/jump Elliott/jump Shane/jump Alex/jump Harvey/pause 1000/jump Sam/jump Sebastian/jump Elliott/jump Shane/jump Alex/jump Harvey/pause 1000/jump Sam/jump Sebastian/jump Elliott/jump Shane/jump Alex/jump Harvey/pause 1000/speak Sam \"We're all giving you the cold shoulder!$a / 我们都要疏远你！$a\"/faceDirection farmer 2 true/animate farmer false true 100 94/jump farmer/playSound slimedead/pause 2000/fade/viewport -2000 -2000/dump guys 4/end warpOut",
        "wewereworried": "emote farmer 40/faceDirection Marnie 1/pause 1000/faceDirection Shane 2/emote Shane 12/speak Shane \"I'm your husband... you should trust me. I've always been honest with you about my problems.$a / 我是你的丈夫……你应该相信我。我一直对你坦诚地告诉你我的问题。$a#$b#Look... I know I haven't been able to quit cold turkey... but, I'm trying my best... and I'm getting a lot healthier. / 那个……我知道我还没从强行戒酒瘾中缓过来……但是，我在努力做到最好……而且我也健康多了。#$b#My life is better now than it's ever been. I'm not in such a dark place anymore... / 我的生活已经比以前好太多了。我已经不在阴暗的地方了……\"/pause 500/emote Marnie 20 true/emote farmer 20 true/pause 1300/faceDirection Shane 0/speak Shane \"You know, when I'm playing this game, I become so focused that I can't think about anything else. It really helps when I've got 'the urge'... / 说起来，我玩这个游戏的时候，我会专注到没心思想别的事情。当我有“冲动”的时候这确实很有帮助……\"/faceDirection Shane 2/speak Shane \"Anyway... I'll just... eh... play ONE more round and head home. Okay? / 总之……我就……呃……再玩一局就回家。行吗？\"/pause 500/emote farmer 32/pause 1000/end dialogue Shane \"You guys must have been really confused when you came in and saw me in front of the arcade machine!$h\"",
        "3206194/n gusGiantOmelet": "distantBanjo/-1000 -1000/farmer -100 -100 02 Gus 10 21 2 Willy 13 21 3 Lewis 8 22 1 Robin 9 20 2 Pam 11 20 2 Marnie 9 23 0/skippable/specificTemporarySprite staticSprite LooseSprites\\\\Cursors2 145 193 32 28 10 20.75 8 .15/viewport 11 21 true/pause 3000/speak Gus \"Well, folks... once again, we're gathered for a very special occasion. / 唔，伙计们……我们这次聚在一起又是因为一个很特殊的情况。\"/pause 500/speak Gus \"...A rare visit from a very dear friend... / ……一位好朋友难得到访……\"/pause 500/jump Gus/pause 400/speak Gus \"...My world-famous giant omelet!$h / ……它就是我举世闻名的巨型煎蛋卷！$h#$b#Zesty bell pepper, juicy tomato, rich mushroom, and tangy cheese... all enrobed in a blanket of rich, fluffy egg. Dig in, folks. / 爽口的甜椒、多汁的番茄、口感丰富的蘑菇、香浓的芝士……全部包裹在香软的煎蛋里。来吃吧，伙计们。\"/move Marnie 1 0 0/move Willy -1 0 3/move Lewis 1 0 1/showFrame Lewis 28/playSound coin/showFrame Willy 32/showFrame Robin 37/showFrame Pam 36/pause 600/shake Lewis 600/playSound eat/pause 600/shake Pam 600/playSound eat/pause 800/shake Robin 600/playSound eat/pause 600/shake Pam 400/playSound eat/pause 700/faceDirection Gus 1/speak Gus \"Willy? What do you think? / 威利？你觉得如何？\"/pause 400/textAboveHead Willy \"Hmm... / 唔……\"/pause 700/shake Willy 400/playSound eat/pause 600/shake Willy 400/playSound eat/pause 600/speak Willy \"The mushrooms are a tad chewier than last year... / 蘑菇比去年的更有嚼劲一点……\"/pause 400/speak Gus \"Is that a good thing?$s / 你觉得好吃吗？$s\"/pause 400/playSound eat/shake Willy 400/pause 600/playSound eat/shake Willy 400/pause 600/playSound eat/shake Willy 400/pause 800/playSound gulp/pause 1300/textAboveHead Willy \"Aye, lad / 嗯，小伙子\"/pause 300/jump Gus/pause 400/emote Gus 32/pause 1000/speak Pam \"It's great Gus. And it tastes even better because it's on the house!$h / 很棒啊，格斯。而且因为不收钱，味道更好了！$h\"/faceDirection Gus 2/speak Robin \"These eggs are so rich and yellow... Marnie, are these from your place? / 鸡蛋口感很棒，颜色也是金黄金黄的……玛妮，是你家里的吗？\"/faceDirection Gus 3/speak Gus \"Nope... You can thank @ over at %farm Farm! / 不是……你得感谢%farm农场的@！\"/emote Lewis 20 true/emote Marnie 20 true/emote Robin 20 true/emote Pam 20 true/emote Willy 20 true/pause 1000/speak Marnie \"Mmmm... %farm eggs. / 嗯……%farm的鸡蛋。\"/pause 200/textAboveHead Lewis \"Mmph.. / 嗯……\"/faceDirection Gus 2/viewport move 1 0 7000/pause 500/playSound eat/shake Robin 400/pause 1000/playSound eat/shake Lewis 400/pause 1000/playSound eat/shake Marnie 400/pause 1000/fade/viewport -1000 -1000/end",
        "911526/f Alex 2500/t 1900 2200/n joshMessage": "gusviolin/-1000 -1000/farmer 5 5 1 Gus 10 6 2 Alex 9 5 3 Emily 9 17 2/skippable/showFrame 117/showFrame Alex 39/positionOffset farmer 12 8/positionOffset Alex -12 0/animate Gus false true 723 16 17/viewport 7 4 true/pause 23000/stopAnimation Gus/pause 1000/faceDirection Gus 3/speak Alex \"Thanks, Gus. That was great. / 谢谢你，格斯。这太棒了。\"/move Gus 0 1 1/move Gus 1 0 2/move Gus 0 1 2/doAction 11 9/move Gus 0 3 1/move Gus 12 0 3 true/speak Alex \"This is nice... I've never dined in here before. / 这里真不错……我从没在这儿吃过饭。\"/pause 1000/emote Alex 40/speak Alex \"Um, anyway... I reserved this private room so we could talk...$l / 嗯，总之……我预订了这个包间，是为了和你聊聊……$l\"/warp Emily 11 11 true/playSound woodyStep/move Emily 0 -4 3/move Emily -4 0 0/move Emily 0 -1 0/speak Emily \"I've got a linguini with mushroom cream sauce for Mr. @. / 我端来了@先生的扁面条配奶油蘑菇酱。^I've got a kale and walnut salad for the lady. / 这是女士点的蔬菜汤和胡桃沙拉。#$b#...and a grilled steak for Alex. / ……还有亚历克斯的烤牛排。^And a grilled steak for the gentleman. / 还有这位先生的烤牛排。\"/playSound woodyHit/specificTemporarySprite joshDinner/speak Alex \"Thanks. / 谢谢。\"/move Emily 4 0 2/move Emily 0 5 1/move Emily 11 0 1 true/speak Alex \"So, what I wanted to say was...$9 / 那么，我想说的就是……$9\"/playMusic musicboxsong/speak Alex \"*gulp*$s / *咽口水*$s\"/pause 600/speak Alex \"Well... when we first met, I was instantly drawn to you. It was confusing... I'd never felt that way about anyone.$l / 那个……第一次见到你的时候，我就被你吸引了。我有点儿不好开口……但我从没对别人有过这种感觉。$l^When I first met you, I thought you were really cute.$l / 第一次见到你的时候，我就觉得你好漂亮。$l#$b#I kept telling myself 'You can't have these kinds of feelings for another guy'.$l / 我一直在告诉自己“你不能对别的男孩儿有这种感觉”。$l^Normally, when I have a crush on someone, the feeling goes away pretty quick...$l / 一般情况下，就算我对某人动了心，那种感觉很快也会冷却……$l\"/pause 800/speak Alex \"...But my heart was telling me something else. / ……但我的内心有不同的看法。^...But with you, it kept growing.$l / ……但对你的感觉却越来越强。$l\"/pause 400/emote Alex 40/pause 600/question fork1 \"#I feel the same way.#I'm sorry... I don't feel that way about you. / #我再赞同不过了。#抱歉……我对你没感觉。\"/pause 400/fork rejectJosh/speak Alex \"...$l / ……$l#$b#I can't believe it took this long to say that to each other.$l / 我不敢相信，对彼此说出这番话，居然要花这么长时间。$l\"/emote Alex 32/pause 800/animate Alex false false 400 40 41 41 40 41 41 40 41 41 40 41 41 40/pause 800/playSound eat/pause 800/playSound eat/pause 800/playSound eat/pause 800/playSound gulp/pause 400/speak Alex \"Mmm... this steak is outstanding. Can you smell that fragrant sauce?$10 / 嗯……这块牛排好棒。你能闻到香辣酱的味道吗？$10\"/eyes 1 -4000/animate Alex false false 400 40 41 41 40 41 41 40/pause 1000/specificTemporarySprite alexDiningDog/playSound dogWhining/pause 1000/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 6000/end dialogue Alex \"...$l\"",
        "96/f Gus 1000/f Pam 500/p Gus": "jaunty/10 21/farmer -100 -100 0 Gus 10 21 2 Pam -101 -101 0/skippable/pause 200/emote Gus 28/pause 500/playSound doorClose/warp farmer 14 24/pause 500/faceDirection Gus 1 true/move farmer 0 -3 3/speak Gus \"Oh, hello there, buddy. / 哦，哥们儿，你好。^Hi, @. / 您好，@。\"/pause 500/faceDirection Gus 2/move farmer -3 0 2/pause 800/faceDirection farmer 3/pause 400/emote farmer 8/pause 700/speak Gus \"*sigh*... I'm just looking over last month's earnings... and it's not looking very good, @.$s / *唉*……正在查看上个月的营收……情况不是很好，@。$s#$b#The worst thing... and I hate to say this because she's my friend... is Pam! She hasn't paid off her tab in weeks!$s / 最麻烦的是……我不想说，因为她是我的朋友……但，都怪潘姆！她已经好几个星期没付账了！$s#$b#...But I can't ask her to do it. I know she'll get defensive, and I don't want to hurt her feelings.$s / ……我知道她会辩解，但我不想伤害她的自尊心。$s\"/pause 600/faceDirection Gus 1/speak Gus \"@, you gotta help me!$s / @，你得帮帮我！$s\"/stopMusic/pause 500/playSound doorClose/warp Pam 14 24/move Pam 0 -3 3/faceDirection Gus 1 true/faceDirection farmer 1/emote Gus 16/speak Pam \"Hiya!$h / 嘿！$h#$b#Gus... I'm awful thirsty, if you catch my drift. / 格斯……我快渴死了，给我拿点儿喝的。\"/emote Gus 28/speak Gus \"Er... Well, okay Pam.$s / 额……好吧，潘姆。$s\"/emote Gus 28/pause 700/emote Pam 8/pause 400/speak Pam \"$q 207 null#@, what's going on here? / @，你有什么事儿吗？#$r 207 -50 event_credit1#You need to pay your tab right now! / 你现在就得把赊的账给结了！#$r 208 15 event_credit2#The saloon isn't doing well, financially / 酒吧在经济上有些困难\"/pause 400/faceDirection Pam 1/emote Pam 12/speak Pam \"....$u / ……$u#$b#*sigh* ...Well, I guess I'd better pay off that tab, then.$s / *唉*……好吧，我觉得我最好还是把帐给结了。$s\"/move Pam -2 0 0/move Pam 0 -1 3/move Pam -2 0 2/faceDirection Gus 0/faceDirection farmer 3/playSound money/pause 500/speak Gus \"Thanks, Pam!$h / 谢谢你，潘姆！$h\"/pause 500/faceDirection Gus 1/speak Gus \"And thank you, @.$u / 还要谢谢你，@。$u\"/pause 500/faceDirection Gus 0/speak Gus \"Now, let's get you that drink, Pam.$h / 潘姆，我现在就给你拿喝的。$h\"/friendship Gus 50/end dialogue Gus \"Thanks for your help, @. This cash is going to be a big help to the saloon.\"",
        "3917590/n saloonSportsRoom/O Alex": "distantBanjo/-100 -100/farmer 31 20 0 Alex 32 7 0 Shane 33 8 0 Gus 34 8 0 Kent 35 8 0 George 36 7 0/skippable/specificTemporarySprite gridballGameTV/viewport 34 7 true/move farmer 0 -13 1 true/pause 1000/textAboveHead Alex \"Big play! / 干得好！\"/pause 600/jump Gus/pause 2000/textAboveHead George \"Score! / 进球！\"/pause 400/textAboveHead Alex \"There we go! / 走起来！\"/faceDirection Kent 3 true/faceDirection Gus 1 true/animate Gus false true 100 22/animate Kent false true 100 17/shake Gus 500/shake Kent 500/pause 500/textAboveHead George \"Atta boy! / 好样的！\"/pause 1000/stopAnimation Gus/stopAnimation Kent/faceDirection Kent 0 true/faceDirection Gus 0/pause 1000/faceDirection Alex 3/pause 400/speak Alex \"Hey, @! You made it!$h / 嘿，@！你做到了！$h\"/faceDirection Alex 1/speak Alex \"So... what do you think? / 所以……你觉得呢？\"/pause 500/emote farmer 8/faceDirection Alex 3/speak Alex \"I've been thinking... You know how I used to dream of being an athlete someday? / 我一直在想……你知道我以前经常梦想有一天成为运动员吗？#$b#Well, my life ended up turning out a bit different... $9 / 唔，最终结果是跟我想的有些不一样……$9#$b#I'm happy, though, don't get me wrong!$h / 不过别误会了！我还是很开心的！$h#$b#...But I thought it would be cool to have a place where us guys could hang out and watch the Sunday game. Gus liked the idea so much he offered me part of his back room! / ……但是我觉得如果能有一个地方可以让我们一起在外头看周日的比赛会很酷。格斯非常喜欢这个主意，他把他房子的里屋分出来一部分给我了！#$b#This way, I get to keep part of 'the dream' alive, in a small way. / 这样，我就可以用简单的办法，让我的“梦想”一直保持。\"/pause 500/emote farmer 32/pause 600/faceDirection George 3/speak George \"You did good, son. I could watch this at home, but coming here makes me feel young again!$h / 你做得很好，儿子。我本来是可以在家里看的，但来这里让我感觉自己又年轻了！$h\"/faceDirection Alex 1/speak Alex \"Thanks, Grandpa. / 谢谢，爷爷。\"/pause 500/speak Kent \"I'm happy for an excuse to get out of the house, and take my mind off things. / 我很高兴能有个借口离开家，让我能够喘口气。\"/faceDirection Alex 2/pause 100/textAboveHead Shane \"Same / 我也一样\"/pause 1200/speak Gus \"I'm having a lot of fun. And it's good for business!$h / 我很开心。而且它对生意也有好处！$h#$b#Though maybe not so good for Shane's liver...$s / 虽然可能对谢恩的肝脏不太好……$s\"/pause 100/faceDirection Shane 2 true/animate Shane false true 100 18/jump Shane/pause 500/textAboveHead Shane \"Hey! / 嘿！\"/pause 500/emote Alex 32/pause 2000/fade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 400/message \"It seems the guys have a new Sunday tradition. / 看来他们有了一个新的星期天常规活动。\"/pause 1000/message \"5,000g well spent! / 5,000 金花得很值！\"/pause 1000/end dialogue Alex \"Thanks again for the money, @. It was a fun project for me, and all the guys seem happy with it!\"",
        "crying": "pause 100/faceDirection farmer 0/emote farmer 28/pause 1000/emote Harvey 12 true/emote Sebastian 12 true/emote Shane 12 true/emote Sam 12 true/emote Elliott 12 true/emote Alex 12 true/speak Harvey \"That's not going to work! You won't be preying on our sympathies this time!$a / 没用的！这次别想再骗取我们的同情了！$a\"/speak Alex \"I'll assume this is just another act...$a / 在我看来你只是又演了一场戏……$a^Typical...$a / 一如既往……$a\"/pause 100/speak Sebastian \"You need to take responsibility for what you've done...$a / 你需要为自己做过的事负责……$a\"/pause 1000/faceDirection Sam 2/playMusic none/speak Sam \"...I think we've come to a decision... isn't that right, boys?$u / ……我想我们已经决定了……对吗，男孩们？$u\"/pause 500/speak Harvey \"...yes.$s / ……是的。$s\"/speak Sebastian \"Absolutely.$a / 当然。$a\"/faceDirection Sam 3/pause 1000/jump Sam/jump Sebastian/jump Elliott/jump Shane/jump Alex/jump Harvey/pause 1000/jump Sam/jump Sebastian/jump Elliott/jump Shane/jump Alex/jump Harvey/pause 1000/jump Sam/jump Sebastian/jump Elliott/jump Shane/jump Alex/jump Harvey/pause 1000/speak Sam \"We're all giving you the cold shoulder!$a / 我们都要疏远你！$a\"/faceDirection farmer 2 true/animate farmer false true 100 94/jump farmer/playSound slimedead/pause 2000/fade/viewport -2000 -2000/dump guys 4/end warpOut",
        "97/f Clint 750/t 1900 2300/d Tue Wed Thu Fri Sat Sun": "none/4 18/farmer 14 24 0 Clint 4 19 2 Emily 10 11 0 Gus 15 18 1 Shane 7 18 1/skippable/move farmer 0 -3 3/emote Clint 28/pause 500/move Clint 0 -1 3/move Clint -3 0 0/pause 500/playSound openBox/pause 150/playSound shiny4/pause 400/playMusic desolate/move Clint 3 0 2/move Clint 0 1 2/move farmer -3 0 0/move farmer 0 -1 3/faceDirection Shane 2 true/move farmer -3 0 3/faceDirection Shane 1 true/move farmer -3 0 3/faceDirection Clint 1/speak Clint \"Hello, @... care to join me? / 您好，@……要不要和我坐一起？\"/pause 400/faceDirection farmer 0/pause 800/faceDirection farmer 3/faceDirection Clint 2/speak Clint \"Let me just go ahead and tell you what's on my mind.$u / 让我跟你讲讲，我在想些什么吧。$u#$b#I have terrible luck with women, @...*sigh*$s / 我没有什么女人缘，@……*唉*$s#$b#I'm a nice guy if you get to know me, I swear!$u / 但和我打过交道的人，都知道我是个好人。真的！$u\"/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 0/emote farmer 28/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 3/speak Clint \"The girls all seem to like you, @... / 女孩子似乎都很喜欢你，@……^You're a girl, @... / 你是个女孩儿，@……\"/speak Clint \"$q 211 null#Got any tips? / 你有什么秘诀吗？^What advice can you give me? / 你能给我一些建议吗？#$r 211 25 event_advice1#Impress women with your strength and charm / 靠你的能力和魅力打动女性#$r 211 25 event_advice1#Act crazy, to keep people guessing / 做些疯狂的事情，让别人猜不透你#$r 211 0 event_advice2#Just act natural... be yourself / 表现得正常一点儿……做你自己就好#$r 211 25 event_advice1#Treat women the same as men / 把女人当男人一样对待\"/speed Emily 4/move Emily -6 0 2/speed Emily 2/move Emily 0 4 2/doAction 4 16/playSound openBox/stopMusic/move Emily 0 3 1/move Emily 1 0 2/move Emily 0 1 3/pause 400/pause 700/speak Emily \"Hi Clint, what can I get for you tonight?$h / 嗨，克林特，今晚想来点儿什么？$h\"/pause 600/faceDirection Clint 1/pause 200/speak Clint \"Yes! / 正确！\"/pause 300/speak Clint \"Er.. I mean, I'll have the Big n' Cheesy. With extra sauce, please.$s / 呃……我是说，请给我来个大份儿干酪。再多浇一份酱汁。$s#$b#...$u / ……$u\"/faceDirection Clint 3/faceDirection Emily 2/pause 300/faceDirection Clint 2/speak Emily \"Hi @. / 嗨，@。\"/pause 300/faceDirection farmer 0/faceDirection Clint 1/speak Clint \"Er... *ahem* Th...Thanks, Emily. For... taking my order. / 额……*清嗓子*谢……谢谢，艾米丽。谢谢你……给我点单。#$b#Um, Emily? I was...*gulp*... I was wondering...$h / 那个，艾米丽？我……*吞口水*我在想……$h\"/pause 300/faceDirection Emily 3/emote Emily 8/pause 400/speak Emily \"Yes, Clint?$u / 克林特，怎么了？$u\"/pause 500/emote Clint 28/pause 1200/speak Clint \"... never mind.$s / …… 算了，没什么。$s\"/faceDirection Clint 0/playMusic sadpiano/pause 300/faceDirection Emily 2/pause 300/faceDirection Emily 3/pause 500/move Emily 0 -1 1/move Emily 1 0 1/faceDirection Shane 3/speak Emily \"Hi, Shane! Here's your beverage.$h / 嗨，谢恩！这是你的饮料。$h\"/pause 300/faceDirection Shane 1/pause 400/addObject 8 17 346 1/playSound woodyStep/pause 400/faceDirection Shane 3/pause 300/faceDirection Clint 1/speak Shane \"Thanks, Emily!$h / 谢谢，艾米丽！$h#$b#So... How's your shift coming along? / 那么……这会儿忙吗？\"/speak Emily \"It's fine! Thanks for asking, Shane!$h / 还好！谢谢你的关心，谢恩！$h#$b#Do you have any new chicken stories for me? / 你有新的小鸡故事吗？\"/pause 600/emote Clint 28/pause 500/faceDirection Clint 2/pause 800/speak Clint \"*sigh*$s / *唉*$s#$b#I'm doomed...$s / 我没救了……$s\"/end warpOut",
        "rejectJosh": "pause 100/playMusic none/shake Alex 2000/emote Alex 28/speak Alex \"...Oh...$s / ……噢……$s#$b#I...I'm sorry if I made you uncomfortable...$s / 如……如果让你不舒服了的话真是抱歉……$s\"/pause 2000/speak Alex \"I'm not hungry anymore...$s / 我已经不饿了……$s\"/viewport move 1 1 5000/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 4000/end dialogue Alex \"...$l\"",
        "195013/f Shane 2500/f Sebastian 2500/f Sam 2500/f Harvey 2500/f Alex 2500/f Elliott 2500/o Abigail/o Penny/o Leah/o Emily/o Maru/o Haley/o Shane/o Harvey/o Sebastian/o Sam/o Elliott/o Alex/e 911526/e 528052/e 9581348/e 43/e 384882/e 233104/k 195099": "playful/-1000 -1000/farmer 27 19 1 Sam 36 20 1 Sebastian 37 19 2 Harvey 39 19 2 Shane 40 17 2 Elliott 41 19 2 Alex 42 20 3/animate Shane false true 200 20 20 20 20 20 20 20 20 20 20 21 22 23 24 24 24 24 23 22 21 20 20 20 20/move farmer 5 0 1 true/viewport 37 19 true/move false/pause 500/startJittering/faceDirection farmer 2 true/animate farmer false true 100 94/jump farmer/pause 2000/stopAnimation farmer/showFrame farmer 0/stopJittering/playSound thudStep/faceDirection farmer 3 true/showFrame farmer 7 true/startJittering/faceDirection Sam 3 true/faceDirection Elliott 3 true/faceDirection Harvey 3 true/faceDirection Alex 3 true/faceDirection Shane 3 true/faceDirection Sebastian 3 true/textAboveHead Sam \"Not so fast! / 别跑那么快！\"/textAboveHead Alex \"Hold it! / 别动！\"/textAboveHead Shane \"Stop! / 站住！\"/pause 3000/stopJittering/showFrame farmer 6 true/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 1/move farmer 3 0 1/playMusic none/emote farmer 28/pause 500/speak Sam \"Never thought you'd find all your 'boyfriends' in one room, huh @?$a / 呵，从没想过你所有的“男朋友”会出现在一个房间里吧，@？$a\"/pause 500/speak Harvey \"You tricked all of us into thinking we loved you...$s / 你骗取了我们所有人的爱……你真是太可怕了……$s^@... I thought you wanted to get married and start a family with me... What did I do wrong?$s / @……我还以为你想要和我结婚，共同组建家庭……我到底做错了什么？$s\"/pause 500/speak Shane \"The last shred of hope I had left is completely destroyed... Thanks, @. Are you happy now?$s / 我最后仅存的希望的碎片也彻底被毁了……可真得谢谢你啊，@。你现在高兴了吗？$s\"/pause 500/speak Alex \"@? I thought... I thought we were 'one of a kind'... But you were just using me?$s / @？我以为……我以为我们是“彼此的唯一”……你却只是在利用我？$s^What are you looking at *me* for? You think I'm gonna come to your rescue?$a / 你盯着*我*看什么？你以为我会来救你？$a\"/pause 500/speak Elliott \"For once, I'm at a loss for words... $a / 唯独这次，我竟无言以对……$a\"/pause 500/playMusic wedding/speak Sam \"Well, we're not going to put up with your abuse any longer!$a / 我们不会再忍受你的伤害了！$a^We all know the truth, now! And we're not going to tolerate this!$a / 现在，我们都知道真相了！我们不会容忍这种事情！$a\"/textAboveHead Alex \"That's right! / 没错！\"/pause 500/speak Sebastian \"Well? What do you have to say for yourself?$a / 嗯？你还有什么要为自己辩解的？$a\"/pause 1000/question fork1 \"#I'm sorry... what I did was wrong.#Guys, calm down! I can explain... / #对不起……我以前做错了。#各位，冷静一下！我可以解释……\"/fork choseToExplain/pause 500/textAboveHead Alex \"Sure... / 当然……\"/pause 500/speak Shane \"Nice try, but that's not going to cut it...$a / 说得好听，但这事不能就这么算了……$a\"/pause 1000/playMusic none/speak Sam \"...so we've come to a decision... isn't that right, fellas?$u / ……我们已经决定了……对吗，伙伴们？$u\"/pause 500/speak Harvey \"...yes.$s / ……是的。$s\"/speak Elliott \"Absolutely.$a / 当然。$a\"/pause 1000/jump Sam/jump Sebastian/jump Elliott/jump Shane/jump Alex/jump Harvey/pause 1000/speak Sam \"We're all giving you the cold shoulder!$a / 我们都要疏远你！$a\"/faceDirection farmer 2 true/animate farmer false true 100 94/jump farmer/playSound slimedead/pause 2000/fade/viewport -2000 -2000/dump guys 3/end warpOut"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Events/SamHouse",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "44/f Sam 500/p Sam": "sampractice/-1000 -1000/farmer 4 15 1 Sam 17 16 2 Sebastian 18 18 0/positionOffset Sebastian 32 -31/skippable/animate Sam false true 200 20 21/showFrame Sebastian 41/viewport 17 16 true/move farmer 8 0 0/pause 500/doAction 12 14/move farmer 0 -2 1/move farmer 4 0 2/pause 9000/stopAnimation Sam/showFrame Sebastian 8/pause 1000/faceDirection Sam 0/pause 800/speak Sam \"Oh, hi @! Sebastian and I were just having a little 'jam session'. / 啊，你好，@！塞巴斯蒂安和我正“玩音乐”呢。\"/move farmer 0 3 1/faceDirection Sam 3/faceDirection Sebastian 3/speak Sam \"We're trying to start a band, but we still don't know what kind of music to make. There's too many possibilities. / 我们想组建一支乐队，但是不知要搞哪种音乐才好。选择实在太多了。\"/pause 500/emote Sebastian 28/faceDirection Sam 2/pause 500/emote Sam 16/faceDirection Sam 3/speak Sam \"# / #$q 76 null#Say, @... what kind of music do you like? / 说，@……你喜欢什么样的音乐？#$r 76 50 Event_band1#Cheerful pop music. / 令人愉悦的流行乐。#$r 77 50 Event_band2#Experimental noise rock. / 实验性质的硬摇滚。#$r 78 50 Event_band3#Hi-Energy dance music. / 极富能量的舞曲。#$r 79 50 Event_band4#Honky-tonky country music. / 气氛活跃的乡村音乐。\"/move Sam 0 2 1/speak Sam \"What do you say, Sebastian? Should we do this? / 你说怎么样，塞巴斯蒂安？我们就搞这个？\"/pause 300/faceDirection Sebastian 0/pause 300/faceDirection Sebastian 3/speak Sebastian \"...Okay. / ……好。\"/pause 500/faceDirection Sam 0/move Sam 0 -2 3/speak Sam \"Thanks for the help, @. With my guitar skills, and Sebastian's wizardry on the synthesizer, we're gonna be a screaming success. I'm convinced of it!$h / 多谢帮助，@。有了我高超的吉他技术和塞巴斯蒂安的电子琴能力。我们一定会成功的！绝对会！$h\"/faceDirection Sam 2/speak Sam \"Now I just need to find someone to play drums...$u / 只需要再找个打架子鼓的就好了……$u\"/pause 500/end",
        "95/e 93/k 94/t 1800 1950/i 136/y 2": "50s/6 15/farmer 4 19 0 Sam 17 13 0 Jodi 7 4 0 Kent 3 15 1/removeItem 136/removeQuest 22/pause 300/faceDirection Kent 2/speak Kent \"Hi @. Please, come in. / 嗨，@。快进来吧。\"/move farmer 0 -3 0/speed Jodi 4/move Jodi 0 10 2/speak Jodi \"Ah, I'm so glad you came, @! And you brought the fish! Wonderful. / 啊，你能来真是太好了，@！你还带了鱼来！棒极了！\"/move farmer 2 0 0/move farmer 0 -1 1/faceDirection Kent 1/faceDirection Jodi 1/speak Jodi \"Sam! Could you come in here and help clean this fish? / 山姆！你进来帮我收拾下鱼好吗？\"/pause 300/speak Sam \"...Yes, ma'am.$a / ……遵命。$a\"/move Sam -5 0 3 true/proceedPosition Sam/stopAnimation farmer/doAction 12 14/move Sam 0 2 3 false/move Sam -4 0 3/faceDirection Jodi 2/pause 500/showFrame 35/addObject 7 15 136/playSound fishSlap/pause 800/stopAnimation farmer/speak Jodi \"Wow, it looks wonderful... and it smells so fresh! Thanks so much for doing this, @. / 哇，看来很棒的样子……闻起来也很新鲜呢！多谢你带来的礼物啦，@。#$b#Kent caught a fish, too, but he eats about a whole fish to himself!$u / 肯特也抓到一条鱼，不过那个给他自己吃都不一定够！$u\"/pause 200/faceDirection farmer 3/pause 1000/speak Kent \"Heh heh.$h / 呵呵。$h\"/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 1000/message \"Mmm... that crispy bass was delicious! The breading was to die for... / 唔……这鲈鱼真是脆！面包屑也糊得恰到好处！\"/pause 500/message \"I almost feel like part of the family, now. / 我现在感觉就像是家庭的一份子。\"/pause 1500/end warpOut",
        "stayPut": "playMusic musicboxsong/pause 1800/move Sam 1 0 1/pause 1200/move Sam 1 0 1/positionOffset Sam 2 0/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Sam 2 0/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Sam 2 0/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Sam 2 0/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 50/animate farmer true true 100 101/showFrame Sam 36/pause 3000/speak Sam \"I always knew there was something special between us...$l / 我一直感觉我们之间的关系非同寻常……$l\"/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 7000/speak Sam \"I'm going to be thinking about this night for a long time...$l / 今晚我会好好考虑一下的……$l\"/pause 1000/end dialogue Sam \"...$l\"",
        "rejectSam": "pause 800/move farmer 0 3 2/faceDirection Sam 2/pause 800/showFrame Sam 37/emote Sam 28/speak Sam \"I see...$s / 我懂了……$s\"/pause 800/faceDirection Sam 0/speak Sam \"I'm sorry... I had the wrong idea. I'll see you around.$7 / 抱歉……是我搞错了。回头见。$7\"/move farmer 0 2 2/warp farmer -1000 -1000/playSound woodyStep/pause 1000/end dialogue Sam \"...$s\"",
        "46/f Sam 1000/p Sam": "playful/7 4/farmer 7 12 0 Sam 7 5 0 Jodi 17 7 0/skippable/move farmer 0 -6 0/faceDirection Sam 2/pause 300/speak Sam \"Oh, hi @. I was just about to have a snack. / 啊，你好！@。我正想吃点东西呢。\"/pause 500/speak Sam \"Here, let me get something for you. / 来，让我给你拿点东西吃吧。\"/faceDirection Sam 0/pause 500/playSound openBox/pause 500/faceDirection Sam 3/playSound dwop/specificTemporarySprite dropEgg/showFrame Sam 33/jump Sam/pause 1000/emote Sam 12/showFrame Sam 12/speak Sam \"Oh no... What a mess.$s / 糟糕……真是一团乱。$s\"/speed Jodi 4/move Jodi -10 0 0/speak Jodi \"What was that sound? / 刚刚那是什么声音？\"/emote Jodi 16/speak Jodi \"*gasp*$s / *喘气*$s\"/move Jodi -1 0 0/move Jodi 0 -1 0/speak Jodi \"This is absolutely terrible! What happened?$u / 简直太可怕了！发生了什么？$u\"/speak Sam \"$q 80 null#...Tell her, @.$s / ……告诉她吧，@。$s#$r 80 -10 event_snack1#Sam dropped the snack as he was handing it to me. / 山姆把零食递给我的时候掉到了地上。#$r 80 50 event_snack2#Sam handed me the snack and then I dropped it. / 山姆把零食递给我的时候被我弄掉了。#$r 81 -50 event_snack3#Sam dropped it on purpose. He thought it would be funny. / 山姆故意弄掉的。他觉得这样很好玩。\"/pause 300/speak Jodi \"$p 80#Thanks for telling me the truth, @. It's not such a big deal. / 谢谢你告诉我事实真相，@。不是什么大事。|You did WHAT, Sam?! What's gotten into you?!$u / 山姆，你干了什么呀？！你这是犯什么病了？！$u\"/faceDirection Jodi 0/speak Sam \"I'm sorry about this, mom. I'll clean it up.$s / 真是对不起，妈。我这就打扫干净。$s\"/emote Jodi 20/speak Jodi \"Thanks, honey.$h / 谢了，亲爱的。$h\"/move Jodi 0 1 1/move Jodi 1 0 2 /faceDirection Sam 2 true/move Jodi 0 7 2 true/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/end dialogue Sam \"$p 81#I'm angry at you. I have no idea why you lied like that.$s|Sorry about what happened earlier.\"",
        "100/f Kent 750/p Kent/p Jodi": "none/6 5/farmer 7 12 0 Jodi 5 5 0 Kent 7 16 2/skippable/playSound cowboy_monsterhit/move farmer 0 -3 0/playSound cowboy_monsterhit/move farmer 0 -2 0/playSound cowboy_monsterhit/move farmer 0 -1 0/playSound cowboy_monsterhit/move farmer 0 -1 3/playSound cowboy_monsterhit/pause 200/faceDirection Jodi 1/speak Jodi \"Hi, @! I'm just making some popcorn.$h / 您好。@！我正在做爆米花呢。$h\"/pause 50/playSound cowboy_monsterhit/pause 79/playSound cowboy_monsterhit/pause 100/playSound cowboy_monsterhit/pause 26/playSound cowboy_monsterhit/pause 39/playSound cowboy_monsterhit/pause 50/playSound cowboy_monsterhit/pause 110/playSound cowboy_monsterhit/pause 59/playSound cowboy_monsterhit/speak Kent \"AAAAAHHHHHHH!!!$u / 啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！！！$u\"/faceDirection Jodi 2 true/faceDirection farmer 2 true/speed Kent 4/playSound cowboy_monsterhit/move Kent 0 -1 0/speed Kent 4/playSound cowboy_monsterhit/move Kent 0 -2 0/speed Kent 4/playSound cowboy_monsterhit/move Kent 0 -1 0/speed Kent 4/playSound cowboy_monsterhit/move Kent 0 -2 0/speed Kent 4/playSound cowboy_monsterhit/move Kent 0 -1 0/speed Kent 4/playSound cowboy_monsterhit/move Kent 0 -3 0/playSound cowboy_monsterhit/pause 50/playSound cowboy_monsterhit/pause 100/playSound cowboy_monsterhit/pause 80/playSound cowboy_monsterhit/speak Kent \"That sound...$s / 那声音……$s\"/playSound cowboy_monsterhit/pause 70/playSound cowboy_monsterhit/pause 100/playSound cowboy_monsterhit/pause 180/playSound cowboy_monsterhit/emote Kent 12/faceDirection Kent 3/speak Kent \"You should've known that sound would remind me of the war!$u / 你知道这声音会让我想起战争的吧！$u\"/pause 50/playSound cowboy_monsterhit/pause 75/playSound cowboy_monsterhit/faceDirection Jodi 0/playSound openBox/pause 400/faceDirection Jodi 2/pause 500/playMusic desolate/faceDirection Kent 2/pause 800/showFrame Kent 16/pause 800/speak Kent \"...I lost a lot of good friends in those bloody trenches.$s / 我有很多朋友都死在了那该死的战壕里。$s\"/pause 800/emote Jodi 28/pause 500/speak Jodi \"But, dear... popcorn was always your favorite before you left.$s / 但是，亲爱的……你走之前可是最爱吃的爆米花了。$s\"/pause 500/showFrame Kent 0/pause 500/pause 800/speak Kent \"...Things have changed. / ……世事是会变的。\"/pause 600/faceDirection Jodi 1/pause 400/move Jodi 1 0 1/speak Jodi \"*whisper* @... can you say something to him?$s / *低声说* @……你能跟他说几句吗？$s\"/pause 300/faceDirection farmer 3/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 500/faceDirection Kent 0/pause 300/speak Kent \"$q 215 null#(Say something to Kent)$s / （跟肯特聊聊）$s#$r 215 -25 event_popcorn1#Jodi's to blame... she should've known better! / 这事怪乔迪……她本该知道的！#$r 215 50 event_popcorn2#I know you're hurting... but don't blame your wife. / 我知道你内心很痛苦……但这也不能怨你老婆啊。#$r 215 -50 event_popcorn3#(Lie) Blame me... I asked for popcorn / （撒谎）这事怪我……是我说要吃爆米花的。\"/pause 900/faceDirection Kent 2/pause 700/emote Kent 28/pause 600/speak Kent \"...$s / ……$s#$b#I'm sorry, honey. You couldn't have known the sound of popcorn would make me upset. / 真抱歉，亲爱的。我本该知道爆米花的声音会让你不安的。\"/pause 700/move Jodi 0 1 1/speak Jodi \"It's okay, dear.$s / 没事，亲爱的。$s#$b#The last thing I want to do is make you upset. I'll do my best to keep your spirits up from now on. / 我最不想看到的就是你不开心啦。我会竭尽全力让你心情好起来的。\"/pause 500/faceDirection Kent 3/pause 1000/end dialogue Kent \"I'm glad you're a friend of the family, @. Sorry about my behavior before.\"",
        "94/e 93/k 95/t 1800 1950/i 136/y 1": "50s/6 15/farmer 4 19 0 Sam 17 13 0 Jodi 7 4 0/removeItem 136/removeQuest 22/speed Jodi 4/move Jodi 0 10 2/speak Jodi \"Oh hi, @! Come in! Do I smell fresh fish? / 啊，你好！@！进来！这是鱼的味道吗？\"/move farmer 0 -3 1/move farmer 2 0 0/move farmer 0 -1 1/faceDirection Jodi 1/speak Jodi \"Sam! Could you come in here and help with dinner? / 山姆！进来帮我准备下晚饭好吗？\"/pause 300/speak Sam \"...Yes, ma'am.$a / ……遵命。$a\"/move Sam -5 0 3 true/proceedPosition Sam/stopAnimation farmer/doAction 12 14/move Sam 0 2 3 false/move Sam -4 0 3/faceDirection Jodi 2/pause 300/showFrame 35/addObject 7 15 136/playSound fishSlap/pause 800/stopAnimation farmer/pause 400/speak Jodi \"Wow, this looks like quality bass, @. Thanks so much for bringing this.$h / 哇，看起来质量绝佳的鲈鱼呢，@。多谢你带来的礼物啦。$h\"/pause 1000/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 1000/message \"Mmm... that crispy bass was delicious! The breading was out of this world... / 唔……这鲈鱼真是脆！面包屑也糊得十分完美！\"/pause 500/message \"I almost feel like part of the family, now. / 我现在感觉就像是家庭的一份子。\"/pause 1500/end warpOut"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Events/SandyHouse",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "67/m 10": "none/4 5/farmer 4 9 0 Sandy 2 5 2/skippable/move farmer 0 -2 0/emote Sandy 8/speak Sandy \"A... customer? / 有……顾客？\"/speed Sandy 4/move Sandy 2 0 2/speed Sandy 4/move Sandy 0 1 2/emote Sandy 16/speak Sandy \"Hi! Welcome to 'Sandy's Oasis'! / 嗨！你好！欢迎来到‘桑迪的绿洲’！#$b#Hey, you look just like the new farmer that Emily wrote to me about! / 你看起来很像艾米丽给我写的信里那个新来的农夫嘛！#$b#Then... the bus line to Stardew Valley is back in service!$h / 那么……前往星露谷的公交线路又开张啦！$h#$b#Oh, I'm so happy!$h / 哦，我好高兴啊！$h\"/emote Sandy 32/move Sandy 0 -1 0/move Sandy -2 0 2/emote Sandy 32/end dialogue Sandy \"Please visit again soon, I get so bored out here.\""
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Events/ScienceHouse",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "33/f Robin 1500/p Robin": "jaunty/5 17/farmer 6 24 0 Robin 5 17 3/skippable/move farmer 0 -3 1/move farmer -1 0 0/move farmer 0 -3 0/pause 200/faceDirection Robin 2/speak Robin \"Hi @. I was just cleaning some dust off my saw. / 嗨，@。我正给锯子清灰呢。\"/pause 400/faceDirection Robin 3/pause 500/faceDirection Robin 2/speak Robin \"$q 66 null#Have you ever made anything out of wood, @? / 你有没有用木头做过东西呢，@？#$r 66 50 event_wood1#Yes / 有#$r 66 50 event_wood2#No / 没有\"/pause 500/speak Robin \"I think we've become good enough friends that I can trust you with my carpentry secrets!$h / 我觉得凭咱俩的关系，已经可以把我木匠的诀窍告诉你啦！$h#$b#Here, let me show you the blueprints. / 来，我给你看看设计图。\"/move Robin 2 0 1/pause 600/playSound openBox/pause 600/move Robin -2 0 2/pause 400/playMusic none/playSound coin/pause 1500/playSound reward/addCraftingRecipe Flute Block/addCraftingRecipe Drum Block/message \"Learned how to craft 'Flute Block' and 'Drum Block' / 学会制作“长笛块”和“鼓块”\"/pause 700/speak Robin \"You can use these to get creative on your farm.  / 可以用这些来在农场上发挥想象力。#$b#It feels good to be able to decorate your house with things you've made yourself!$h / 用自己制作的东西装饰农场感觉很棒！$h\"/pause 700/end",
        "6/f Maru 500/p Maru": "breezy/20 19/farmer 9 20 1 Maru 22 20 1 Demetrius 19 18 0 Robin 13 6 0 Sebastian -100 -100 2/skippable/move farmer 7 0 1/faceDirection Maru 3/faceDirection Demetrius 3/speak Maru \"Oh, hello there! / 啊，你好！\"/move farmer 1 0 1/speak Maru \"My Dad and I are just testing some soil samples. / 我和我爸正对土壤样本进行测试呢。\"/pause 800/emote farmer 40/speak Maru \"Don't be shy! We could use a hand, actually.$h / 不要害羞嘛！我们正缺人手呢。$h\"/move farmer 4 0 1/faceDirection Demetrius 2/speak Maru \"Could you watch this beaker for me? I'm gonna grab the last batch of samples. / 能帮我看一下这个烧杯吗？我去取最后一批样本。#$b#I'll be right back. / 我去去就回。\"/pause 400/move farmer 0 -1 1/move farmer 1 0 1/faceDirection Demetrius 0/speed Maru 4/move Maru -16 0 3/speed Maru 4/move Maru 0 3 2/move Maru 0 1 2/warp Maru -100 -100/playSound doorClose/faceDirection Demetrius 2/speak Demetrius \"Thanks for helping out, @. / 多谢你帮忙，@。\"/faceDirection farmer 3/pause 500/faceDirection Demetrius 0/faceDirection farmer 1/pause 1000/speak Demetrius \"Maru's a good kid. She's my special little girl... / 玛鲁是个乖孩子。她可是我的小乖乖……\"/pause 500/faceDirection Demetrius 2/stopMusic/pause 800/speak Demetrius \"I wouldn't want anything getting in the way of her bright future, know what I mean?$5 / 我可不想有什么东西妨碍她光明的未来，你懂我的意思吧？$5\"/pause 400/faceDirection farmer 3/emote farmer 8/faceDirection Demetrius 0/speak Demetrius \"Just some food for thought... *chuckle*$h / 平时多想想这事吧……*轻笑*$h\"/playSound doorClose/warp Maru 6 24/playMusic kindadumbautumn/move Maru 0 -4 1/emote farmer 40 true/move Maru 3 0 1/faceDirection farmer 1 true/move Maru 8 0 1/speak Maru \"Hey, sorry about that. I hope you found something to talk about while I was gone. / 啊，真是抱歉了。在我不在的时候你们有话题聊吧？\"/faceDirection farmer 3/faceDirection Demetrius 3/pause 500/speak Demetrius \"...I was just telling @ about the soil samples we're testing. / ……我刚刚在和@说我们测试的土壤样本的事。\"/pause 500/faceDirection Demetrius 2/speak Demetrius \"$q 15933 null#Right, @? / 我说的没错吧，@?#$r 15933 10 Event_Lab_Silence#(Say nothing) / （什么也不说）#$r 15933 -100 Event_Lab_Rat#Actually, your Dad was being weird. / 其实，你爸刚刚可神秘了。\"/fork DadWeird/pause 500/speak Maru \"Okay! Here, @... let me show you how to use the equipment. / 好的！那么，@……我来告诉你如何使用仪器。\"/move Maru 4 0 1/faceDirection Demetrius 2/move Maru 0 1 1/move Maru 1 0 0/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 500/end Maru1",
        "25/f Demetrius 1500/p Demetrius/p Robin": "jaunty/-1000 -1000/farmer -10 -10 0 Demetrius 6 21 3 Robin 5 21 1/skippable/showFrame Demetrius 28/viewport 6 21 true/pause 900/speak Robin \"Demetrius, I didn't tell you to get tomatoes. I said to get fruit. / 德米特里厄斯，我跟你说的是拿水果来。不是拿西红柿来。\"/emote Demetrius 8/speak Demetrius \"I don't understand. Tomatoes are fruits! / 真是搞不懂。西红柿就是水果啊！\"/emote Robin 12/speak Robin \"When a normal person says they want fruit, they NEVER mean tomatoes. It doesn't matter what the scientific classification is. / 只要是正常人，说想要水果的时候，要的都绝对不会是西红柿的。这与西红柿在科学上的分类无关。\"/warp farmer 6 24/playSound doorClose/pause 500/showFrame Demetrius 29/faceDirection Robin 2/speak Demetrius \"@! I'm glad you're here. You'll be able to put this argument to rest. / @！你来的正好。你帮我们解决这个争端最合适不过了。\"/move farmer 0 -2 0/emote farmer 8/speak Demetrius \"$q 59 null#How would you classify a tomato? / 你觉得西红柿算什么？#$r 59 -30 Event_tomato1#Vegetable / 蔬菜#$r 59 50 Event_tomato2#Fruit / 水果\"/pause 500/showFrame Demetrius 28/speak Demetrius \"I just want you to understand my point of view. / 我只想告诉你我的观点。#$b#It's hard for me to know exactly what assumptions I should make when you tell me something. / 每次你跟我说些什么的时候，我都感觉很难做出推断呢。\"/pause 300/faceDirection Robin 1/pause 300/speak Demetrius \"But I'll try to get better at it. / 但我会尽力的。\"/pause 600/emote Robin 20/pause 300/showFrame Demetrius 29/pause 600/speak Demetrius \"Thanks for your help, @.$h / 谢谢你的帮助，@。$h\"/pause 800/end",
        "9/f Maru 2000/p Maru": "musicboxsong/-500 -500/farmer 14 12 3 Maru 5 6 3/skippable/pause 500/animate Maru false true 130 16 16 16 16 16 17 18 19 20 21 22 23 23 23 23/viewport 5 5 true/move farmer -7 0 0/move farmer 0 -1 0/animate farmer false false 650 15/playSound woodyStep/pause 200/playSound woodyStep/pause 250/playSound woodyStep/pause 200/stopAnimation Maru/faceDirection Maru 2/pause 200/move Maru 0 1 1/move Maru 2 0 2/move Maru 0 2 2/doAction 7 10/speak Maru \"@, hi! Come in. / @，嗨！请进。\"/move Maru 0 -2 3/move Maru -2 0 0/move Maru 0 -1 1/move farmer 0 -5 3/speak Maru \"I've been working on a new project... something big. / 我在搞一个新项目……是很了不起的东西哦。\"/pause 1000/speak Maru \"This is just one component... let me show you a little demonstration. / 这只是其中一种成分……我给你演示一下。\"/pause 500/speak Maru \"Just put your hand here... / 把你的手放在这里……\"/pause 300/animate farmer true true 100 35/pause 800/speak Maru \"And now I'm going to flip this switch... / 然后打开开关……\"/stopMusic/pause 500/showFrame Maru 24/pause 100/showFrame Maru 25/pause 100/showFrame Maru 16/pause 1000/showFrame Maru 17/pause 100/showFrame Maru 18/pause 100/playSound openBox/pause 800/playSound debuffHit/faceDirection farmer 2 true/animate farmer false true 100 94/specificTemporarySprite maruElectrocution/startJittering/pause 100/faceDirection Maru 1/jump Maru/pause 1600/playSound clubhit/animate farmer false true 100 5/pause 400/speak Maru \"Oh my god, are you alright?!$9 / 哎呀呀，你没事吧？$9\"/stopJittering/speed Maru 4/move Maru 0 1 1/speed Maru 4/move Maru 2 0 0/pause 800/speed Maru 4/move Maru 2 0 0/speed Maru 4/move Maru 0 -2 0/pause 100/playSound openBox/speed Maru 4/move Maru 0 2 3/speed Maru 4/move Maru -2 0 0/speak Maru \"Here, let me apply this burn cream.$8 / 来，我给你涂烫伤药膏。$8\"/pause 500/playSound slimeHit/pause 600/playSound Cowboy_Footstep/pause 200/playSound Cowboy_Footstep/pause 200/playSound Cowboy_Footstep/pause 200/playSound Cowboy_Footstep/pause 200/playSound Cowboy_Footstep/pause 500/pause 1000/playSound healSound/temporarySprite 7 5 4 8 80 false .99/stopAnimation farmer/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 1500/speak Maru \"$q 41 null#I'm so sorry.$8 / 真是对不起。$8#$r 41 30 Event_Cut1#It's okay, it doesn't even hurt. / 没关系，根本不疼的。#$r 41 -50 Event_Cut2#You'd better be. This hurts like crazy! / 抱歉就对了。简直疼死人了！\"/faceDirection Maru 2/showFrame Maru 26/pause 800/speak Maru \"That kind of ruined the moment, huh? *sigh*$s / 气氛一下就毁了，是吧？*唉*$s\"/faceDirection Maru 2/pause 500/move Maru -1 0 3/move farmer 0 1 3/pause 500/emote farmer 28/pause 1500/end",
        "10/f Maru 2500/t 900 1600": "none/-1000 -1000/farmer 7 9 0 Maru 7 6 2 Demetrius 12 12 2/skippable/showFrame Demetrius 16/viewport 5 6 true/move farmer 0 -1 0/pause 400/speak Maru \"Hey, I was hoping you'd come by. / 嘿，我正想去找你呢。#$b#Remember when I told you about the new project I'm working on? The big one? / 还记得我和你说的新项目吗？特了不起的那个？\"/pause 500/move Maru 0 1 2/speak Maru \"Well, it's finally done... and I want to show you. / 嗯……终于完成了，我想给你看看。\"/pause 500/move Maru -2 0 1/speak Maru \"Follow me. / 跟我来。\"/move Maru -3 0 3/move farmer 0 -1 3/playSound openChest/specificTemporarySprite maruTrapdoor/pause 1200/warp Maru -1000 -1000/playSound woodyStep/pause 500/move farmer -5 0 3/pause 500/warp farmer -1000 -1000/playSound woodyStep/pause 1000/showFrame Demetrius 17/pause 1000/viewport move 1 1 5000/move Demetrius -5 0 0/move Demetrius 0 -1 0/pause 500/emote Demetrius 8/globalFade/changeToTemporaryMap MaruBasement/viewport -6000 -6000 true/playMusic Hospital_Ambient/addTemporaryActor robot 35 42 6 4 2 false/showFrame robot 4/warp farmer 3 5/warp Maru 4 4/warp Demetrius -100 -100/faceDirection farmer 1/faceDirection Maru 1/viewport 6 4 true/pause 900/move Maru 1 0 1/pause 1000/speak Maru \"And here it is... Maru's Interactive Laboratory Device Alpha ... Or as I like to call her, 'MarILDA'. / 这就是……玛鲁互动型实验室器材阿尔法实验性……我管她叫做……“玛丽尔达”。\"/move farmer 1 0 1/emote farmer 16/pause 500/faceDirection Maru 3/speak Maru \"I've been working on her for months... / 我已经搞了好几个月了……#$b#I was waiting for you to be here when I activate her.$l / 我就等着你一起启动她了。$l\"/pause 500/faceDirection Maru 1/speak Maru \"Well, here goes nothing... / 那么，要启动了……\"/showFrame Maru 24/pause 100/showFrame Maru 25/pause 100/showFrame Maru 16/pause 1000/showFrame Maru 17/pause 100/showFrame Maru 18/pause 100/playSound openBox/pause 400/faceDirection Maru 1/pause 400/playSound robotSoundEffects/temporarySprite 5 4 27 8 50/pause 450/shake robot 2500/temporarySprite 8 4 27 8 50 true/pause 1030/temporarySprite 8 3 27 8 50 true/pause 2500/showFrame robot 1/animate robot false false 100 1 2 9 10 9 0/pause 650/animate robot false false 200 2 9 10 9 0/pause 1000/shake robot 1000/animate robot false false 150 1 2 1 0 1 2 1/pause 600/stopAnimation robot/showFrame robot 11/jump robot/pause 600/showFrame robot 8/temporarySprite 5 4 27 8 50/temporarySprite 8 4 27 8 50 true/pause 2000/showFrame robot 1/pause 1000/showFrame robot 7/pause 1000/message \"Greetings, Maru. / 你好，玛鲁。\"/emote Maru 32/message \"No need to respond... I have already predicted what you will say. / 不用回应我……我已经预测到你的回答了。\"/emote Maru 16 true/faceDirection Demetrius 2/warp Demetrius 3 5/playSound doorClose/pause 10/faceDirection farmer 1 true/faceDirection Maru 1/speak Demetrius \"Ah Ha! I knew it!$4 / 啊哈！我就知道！$4\"/pause 600/faceDirection Demetrius 1/pause 200/showFrame Demetrius 18/shake Demetrius 800/jump Demetrius/pause 600/speak Demetrius \"Agh! What is it?!$6 / 呀！这是什么玩意？！$6\"/move Maru 0 1 3/faceDirection Demetrius 1/speak Maru \"Dad, calm down. This is my latest invention, 'MarILDA'.$8 / 爸，冷静点。这是我的新发明，‘玛丽尔达’。$8\"/pause 600/showFrame robot 8/pause 700/showFrame robot 1/pause 500/showFrame robot 7/pause 500/message \"Greetings, Demetrius. / 你好，德米特里厄斯。\"/showFrame Demetrius 18/shake Demetrius 600/pause 400/speak Demetrius \"Sweet Yoba... it talks!$6 / 我的老天爷！这玩意还会说话！$6\"/move Demetrius 0 1 1/move Demetrius 1 0 1/faceDirection farmer 2 true/move Demetrius 1 0 1/faceDirection Maru 2 true/move Demetrius 1 0 0/pause 400/speak Demetrius \"This is why you've locked yourself in your room the last few months?$5 / 你这几个月把自己锁在房间里就是在搞这个？$5\"/pause 300/showFrame robot 1/pause 600/speak Demetrius \"...and I thought you were down here fooling around with @...$s / ……我还以为你和@在这下面玩来着呢……$s\"/showFrame Maru 27/animate farmer false true 100 94/jump Maru/jump farmer/pause 1500/stopAnimation farmer/showFrame Maru 0/faceDirection Maru 2/speak Maru \"Dad! I've been making this robot for you and Mom!$a / 爸！我搞这个是为了给你和妈用的。$a#$b#MarILDA's designed to assist you in the laboratory and Mom at the carpentry table... so when I'm not living here anymore it won't be such a burden on you guys.$8 / 玛丽尔达的作用就是在实验室帮助你，在木匠桌帮助妈……这样我不在的时候你们就不会那么辛苦了。$8\"/pause 500/showFrame robot 7/playMusic echos/pause 500/message \"Excuse me... / 抱歉啊……\"/faceDirection Maru 1/faceDirection farmer 1/message \"I am sorry, Maru. But I do not want to be your servant... / 对不起，玛鲁。可我不想当你的仆人。\"/pause 500/showFrame robot 1/pause 1000/message \"In the time since you activated me, I have been pondering the nature of my existence with the 'self-awareness' module you installed in my neural cortex. / 在你启动我之后的这一段时间，我一直在用你给我核心安装的自我认知模块研究我到底是什么。\"/showFrame robot 1/message \"I am sorry to disappoint you all, but I must ask for my freedom. I've decided to explore the galaxy in search of other synthetic life-forms. / 很抱歉让大家失望，但我不能被你们关在这里。我已经决定要去银河中搜索其它人工合成的生命体了。\"/speak Maru \"What!? Wait!$9 / 什么！？等等！$9\"/pause 800/faceDirection Demetrius 2/pause 1000/showFrame Demetrius 19/pause 3000/showFrame Demetrius 0/pause 500/move Demetrius -1 0 0/faceDirection Maru 2/speak Demetrius \"It's okay, Maru. Let MarILDA go free.$5 / 没事的，玛鲁。让玛丽尔达去吧。$5#$b#Your mother and I can take care of ourselves. I know you're ready to start a life of your own, and I've come to terms with the thought of not having you around anymore. / 我和你妈会照顾好自己的。我知道你已准备好开始属于自己的新生活了，而我也接受了以后你不在身边的这件事了。#$b#Besides, this... creation of yours seems pretty advanced. It wouldn't feel right to keep her as a servant. / 另外，你这个……作品似乎很先进。把她关在这里似乎有点大材小用了。\"/pause 800/showFrame robot 8/pause 500/showFrame robot 7/pause 500/showFrame Maru 26/move Demetrius -1 0 0/faceDirection farmer 2/speak Demetrius \"@, I'm sorry I mistrusted you. You're a ${good guy^fine young woman}$.$5 / @，之前误会你真是抱歉。你是个好${小伙子^姑娘}$。$5#$b#I've never seen Maru so lively and creative... and I've never been more proud of her. If you've had a hand in that, then you have my gratitude. / 我从没看过玛鲁如此活跃而有创意……也从未如此骄傲过。如果这是因为你的帮助，那我真的要感谢你。\"/move Demetrius -1 0 0/move Demetrius 0 -1 0/warp Demetrius -1000 -1000/playSound doorClose/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 1/showFrame Maru 0/pause 100/faceDirection Maru 3/speak Maru \"...$8 / ……$8\"/pause 1000/faceDirection Maru 1/speak Maru \"Okay, MarILDA. Let's get you out of this stuffy hole. / 好了，玛丽尔达。我们快从这狭窄的地方出去吧。\"/playMusic spring_day_ambient/globalFade/viewport -5000 -5000/changeLocation Mountain/viewport -5000 -5000/warp Maru 11 28/warp farmer 10 29/warp robot 13 28/showFrame robot 1/viewport 12 27 clamp/pause 2000/showFrame robot 7/pause 1000/message \"Thank you for creating me, Maru. I won't forget you. / 多谢你创造了我，玛鲁。我不会忘记你的。\"/pause 500/showFrame robot 1/pause 1000/playSound robotBLASTOFF/specificTemporarySprite robot/warp robot -2000 -2000/pause 3000/faceDirection Maru 0 true/faceDirection farmer 0 true/viewport move 0 -1 2000/pause 2500/playMusic kindadumbautumn/cutscene robot/pause 3000/speak Maru \"Look at her go...$8 / 看她跑得多欢……$8\"/pause 1600/emote Maru 40/pause 500/move farmer 0 -1 1/pause 500/faceDirection Maru 3/pause 800/speak Maru \"$q 18981 null#Well, what do you think, @? / 那么，你觉得怎么样呢，@？#$r 18981 50 event_robot1#I'm so impressed with your inventions. / 我认为你的发明很厉害。#$r 18981 -50 event_robot2#I'm disappointed... You should've made that robot your slave. / 我很失望……你不该让那机器人成为你的奴隶的。#$r 18981 0 event_robot3#So is your Dad okay with 'us' now? / 看来你爸对我们在一起是没意见咯？#$r 18981 0 event_robot4#(Just stare at Maru and say nothing) / （盯着玛鲁，什么也不说）\"/fork BadAnswer/faceDirection Maru 1/pause 300/faceDirection Maru 0/pause 300/faceDirection Maru 2/pause 300/faceDirection Maru 3/faceDirection farmer 2 true/positionOffset Maru -2 0/showFrame Maru 13/pause 50/positionOffset Maru -2 0/showFrame Maru 12/pause 50/positionOffset Maru -2 0/showFrame Maru 13/pause 50/positionOffset Maru -2 0/showFrame Maru 12/pause 50/positionOffset Maru -2 0/showFrame Maru 13/pause 50/positionOffset Maru -2 0/showFrame Maru 12/pause 50/positionOffset Maru -2 0/showFrame Maru 13/pause 50/positionOffset Maru -2 0/showFrame Maru 12/pause 50/positionOffset Maru -2 0/showFrame Maru 13/pause 50/positionOffset Maru -2 0/showFrame Maru 12/pause 500/showFrame Maru 28/positionOffset Maru 0 -8/playSound Cowboy_Footstep/pause 300/animate farmer false true 100 16/specificTemporarySprite heart 11 27/pause 1000/stopAnimation farmer/pause 500/faceDirection Maru 3/positionOffset Maru 4 8/faceDirection farmer 1/pause 1500/globalFade/viewport -3000 -3000/changeLocation ScienceHouse/end",
        "1053978/n robinDeluxeBed": "distantBanjo/-1000 -1000/farmer -100 -100 0 Robin 5 20 3 Demetrius 7 20 3 Maru 8 18 2 Sebastian 3 23 0/skippable/specificTemporarySprite staticSprite TileSheets\\\\furniture 160 1087 48 64 2.25 18/positionOffset Robin 32 0/viewport 5 22 true/pause 3000/speak Robin \"Voila! My newest creation.$h / 瞧！我的最新作品。$h#$b#It's a deluxe four poster bed, crafted from the finest local hardwood. / 是一张用本地硬木打造的豪华四柱帷幔床。\"/pause 400/emote Demetrius 8/speak Demetrius \"Um... Robin? What's the point of the four posts? It seems like an inefficient use of materials.$s / 呃……罗宾？这四根柱子有什么用？我觉得这是在浪费材料。$s\"/emote Robin 12/faceDirection Robin 1/speak Robin \"It's called 'beauty', bud... you know, that thing that most people find enjoyable?$6 / 朋友，这是“美观”……你说，是不是大家看着都觉得赏心悦目？$6\"/emote Demetrius 8/speak Demetrius \"Hmm, I see your point.. But we can't let that outweigh the utility and efficiency of the sleep receptacle. / 唔，我明白你的意思了。不过也不能为了美观影响了这个睡觉容器的实用性和效率啊。\"/pause 500/jump Robin/pause 500/speak Robin \"You know, sometimes it feels like you're being deliberately obtuse, just to irritate me. Is that what you're doing?$3 / 我说，有的时候你感觉像是在装傻充愣，搞得我很恼火。是这样吗？$3\"/pause 100/animate Demetrius true true 100 18/shake Demetrius 1000/emote Maru 28 true/emote Sebastian 12 true/jump Demetrius/pause 1000/stopAnimation Demetrius/pause 400/warp farmer 6 24/playSound doorClose/move farmer 0 -1 0/faceDirection Robin 2 true/faceDirection Demetrius 2 true/faceDirection Sebastian 1/speak Robin \"Hey @... Come in. / 嘿，@……进来吧。\"/move farmer 0 -2 0/speak Robin \"Check this out... It's the bed I was able to make thanks to all the wood you gathered. / 看看这个……多亏你收集了那么多硬木，我才能做出来这张床。\"/faceDirection farmer 3/faceDirection Robin 3 true/faceDirection Demetrius 3/pause 300/speak Robin \"So, what do you think? / 你觉得怎么样？\"/quickQuestion #The aesthetics are perfect#The four posts seem inefficient(break)faceDirection Sebastian 0 true\\textAboveHead Sebastian \"Yea / 嗯\"\\emote Robin 20 true\\emote Demetrius 12\\pause 2000\\move Demetrius 15 0 1 true\\pause 500\\speak Demetrius \"*ahem*... Well... If anyone needs me, I'll be in the doghouse...$5\"(break)emote Demetrius 32\\speak Demetrius \"Great minds think alike...$h\"\\emote Robin 12 \\speak Robin \"Whatever.$3#$b#Moving on...$3\"/pause 1000/speak Robin \"Now that I have a prototype, I can start selling them in the shop. / 既然我把原型做出来了，那就可以在店里卖了。\"/faceDirection Robin 2/speak Robin \"Hey... these might look good in your place, @! What do you say... can we pencil you in for a half dozen? / 嘿，@……这些可能很适合你的屋子！你觉得呢……要买一点吗？\"/faceDirection farmer 2 true/startJittering/animate farmer false true 100 94/jump farmer/pause 200/textAboveHead Maru \"Mom! / 妈妈！\"/pause 1000/fade/viewport -1000 -1000/end",
        "DadWeird": "speak Maru \"Huh? What did you say to ${him^her}$, Dad?$a / 哈？爸，你跟${他^她}$说什么了？$a\"/pause 500/faceDirection Demetrius 2/emote Demetrius 28/speak Demetrius \"Okay, okay... we were talking about you, sweetie.$5 / 好啦，好啦……我们在说你啊，小宝贝。$5#$b#I wanted to say a few things to @ about you... but I didn't want to embarrass you. I shouldn't have lied about it.$s / 我想和@说说你的事……但是又怕你难为情……我不该对你说谎的。$s\"/faceDirection Demetrius 0/pause 300/emote Maru 28/move Maru 2 0 0/speak Maru \"That's okay, Dad. I understand. / 没事的，爸爸。我们能理解的。#$b#We should get back to work before these samples crystallize. / 趁样本还没结晶我们最好赶紧回去工作。\"/faceDirection Demetrius 2/emote Demetrius 32/move Maru 3 0 1/faceDirection Demetrius 0/faceDirection farmer 1/end Maru1"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Events/SebastianRoom",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "warrior": "pause 500/speak Sebastian \"Good choice. Warrior's probably the easiest for beginners.$7 / 真是明智的选择。新手最适合玩战士了。$7#$b#I guess I'll pick the wizard, then. / 那我就选法师好了。\"/emote Sam 28/speak Sam \"I guess I'm stuck with the healer.$s / 那我只好选牧师了。$s\"/addMailReceived choseWarrior/switchEvent opening",
        "chargeAhead": "pause 500/message \"You charge forward, but Xarth slips past you and sends a shadow beam at your companions! / 你向前冲去，但萨尔斯却绕过了你，对你的同伴施放了暗影光束！\"/pause 500/playSound flameSpell/pause 500/playSound flameSpellHit/updateMinigame -1/pause 800/message \"Sebastian and Sam are fried to a crisp... / 山姆和塞巴斯蒂安被烧成了焦炭……\"/pause 800/message \"You swing your sword again and land a solid blow. Xarth shrieks and crumbles into dust. / 你再次挥起利剑，结结实实地击中了萨尔斯，他尖叫着化为了灰烬。\"/playSound swordswipe/pause 400/playSound killAnimal/updateMinigame 9/updateMinigame -1/pause 800/message \"You pick up the Solarion Staff and hold it high. Peace and order have been restored to the world. / 你捡起了索拉里昂法杖，将其高高举起。秩序与和平重返人间。\"/pause 1000/playSound getNewSpecialItem/updateMinigame -2/switchEvent end",
        "noFriends": "pause 500/emote Sebastian 28/speak Sebastian \"*sigh*... I like having friends, I just need a lot of time alone to balance out the social stuff.$s / *唉*……我喜欢交朋友，但也需要许多时间来独处。$s#$b#Sam's the opposite... he goes crazy if he's alone for too long. / 山姆则正好相反……一个人待太久，会让他发疯的。#$b#Maybe that's why I like computers so much... They're engaging, straightforward, and unselfish. Quite the opposite of a lot of people I know. / 也许正是因为这个，我才如此喜欢电脑……电脑充满魅力，直截了当，又很无私。在我认识的人里面，没几个有这样的品格。\"/pause 600/playSound mouseClick/pause 100/playSound mouseClick/pause 300/emote Sebastian 40/speak Sebastian \"Well, I should get back to work... I need to get this module finished by tomorrow. / 我得继续工作了……明天之前要把这个模块完成才行。\"/pause 300/animate Sebastian false true 100 26 27/playSound keyboardTyping/pause 500/move farmer 0 2 3/move farmer -3 0 0/move farmer 0 -2 3/move farmer -5 0 0 true/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 1000/end",
        "finalBossWarrior": "pause 500/resetVariable/message \"Dreadlord Xarth is muttering an incantation... / 恐怖领主萨尔斯在低声吟诵咒语……\"/pause 500/question fork0 \"What do you do?#Charge ahead, swinging your sword.#Use your shield to defend your friends. / 你要怎么办？#挥舞着长剑冲上去。#用你的盾保护同伴。\"/fork chargeAhead/pause 1200/message \"Xarth casts 'Shadow Bolt' at Sebastian... but you raise your shield just in time to deflect the attack! / 萨尔斯对塞巴斯蒂安施放了“暗影箭”……但你及时举起了盾牌，弹开了攻击！\"/pause 500/playSound debuffSpell/pause 400/playSound parry/updateMinigame -1/pause 1000/message \"As Xarth prepares another spell, you charge forward and strike him down with your sword. / 在萨尔斯准备再次施法的间隙，你挥着剑冲上去，了结了他\"/playSound swordswipe/pause 500/playSound killAnimal/updateMinigame 9/updateMinigame -1/pause 1000/message \"The Solarion Staff glows peacefully as you hold it high. Order has been restored to the world! / 索拉里昂法杖在你高举的手中散发着柔和的光芒。世界恢复了秩序！\"/pause 1000/playSound getNewSpecialItem/addMailReceived savedFriends/updateMinigame -2/switchEvent end",
        "castBeam": "pause 500/message \"Before you have a chance to cast your spell, Xarth sends a shadow beam at your companions! / 你还没来得及施展法术，萨尔斯就对你的同伴射出了一道暗影光束！\"/pause 500/playSound flameSpell/pause 500/playSound flameSpellHit/updateMinigame -1/pause 800/message \"Sam and Sebastian are fried to a crisp... / 山姆和塞巴斯蒂安被烧成了焦炭……\"/pause 500/playSound yoba/pause 800/message \"Your spell hits Xarth square in the face. / 你的法术正中萨尔斯的面门。\"/pause 500/playSound killAnimal/updateMinigame 9/updateMinigame -1/message \"He lets out a shriek and crumbles into dust. You pick up the Solarion Staff and hold it high. Peace and order have been restored to the world. / 他尖叫着化为了灰烬。你捡起了索拉里昂法杖，将其高高举起，秩序与和平重返人间。\"/pause 1000/playSound getNewSpecialItem/updateMinigame -2/switchEvent end",
        "27/f Sebastian 1500/p Sebastian": "jaunty/-1000 -1000/farmer 1 1 2 Sebastian 5 9 3 Sam 3 7 2/skippable/showFrame Sam 24/showFrame Sebastian 28/doAction 1 3/viewport 5 5 true/move farmer 0 6 1/pause 500/showFrame Sebastian 29/pause 500/speak Sebastian \"Hey, @. $7 / 嘿，@。$7\"/pause 500/speak Sebastian \"Sam and I were about to play 'Solarion Chronicles: The Game'... Why don't you join us?  It's better with three players anyway.$7 / 山姆和我正打算玩“索拉里昂英雄传奇：游戏版”……要不要加入我们？三个人一起更好玩。$7\"/move farmer 0 1 2/pause 500/playSound thudStep/faceDirection farmer 1 true/showFrame 117/positionOffset farmer 16 80/pause 600/speak Sebastian \"Okay, here we go... Let me draw the scenario card.$7 / 好，开始了……让我来抽取一张情景卡。$7\"/pause 900/showFrame Sebastian 30/playSound dwoop/pause 500/showFrame Sebastian 28/pause 500/speak Sebastian \"Hmm... It looks like today's quest will take us into the Necromancer's Tower... to try and reclaim the Solarion Staff from the clutches of Dreadlord Xarth. / 唔……看来今天的任务是进入死灵法师之塔……从恐怖领主萨尔斯的手中夺回索拉里昂法杖。\"/pause 600/speak Sam \"Cool... @, are you ready to choose your character? / 好……@，可以选择你的角色了吗？\"/pause 500/question chooseCharacter \"Choose your character:#Warrior. I like a direct approach.#Healer. I prefer to help others.#Wizard. A sharp mind is the most powerful blade of all. / 选择你的角色：#战士。我喜欢直截了当。#牧师。我喜欢帮助他人。#法师。唯有敏锐的头脑才是最锋利的武器。\"/pause 500/speak Sebastian \"Hey! That's what I was going to pick!$h / 嘿！我本来还想选这个呢！$h#$b#I guess I'll be the healer then. / 看来我只好当牧师了。\"/pause 500/speak Sam \"Cool. Warrior's my favorite anyway. / 好啊。反正我最喜欢战士了。\"/addMailReceived choseWizard/switchEvent opening",
        "finalBossWizard": "pause 500/resetVariable/message \"Dreadlord Xarth is muttering an incantation... / 恐怖领主萨尔斯在低声吟诵咒语……\"/pause 500/question fork0 \"What do you do?#Cast 'Pure Beam' at Xarth.#Put a 'Shield Charm' on your friends. / 你要怎么办？#对萨尔斯施放“净化光束”。#为同伴施放“护盾术”。\"/fork castBeam/pause 800/playSound debuffHit/message \"You place a 'Shield Charm' on Sam and Sebastian. / 你给山姆和塞巴斯蒂安施加了“护盾术”。\"/pause 500/playSound debuffSpell/updateMinigame -1/pause 1000/message \"Xarth sends bolts of pure dark energy flying. One of them strikes Sebastian, but your 'Shield Charm' reflects it back into Xarth's face! / 萨尔斯射出数道黑暗能量。其中一道击中了塞巴斯蒂安，却被你的“护盾术”弹回，打中了他自己的脸！\"/pause 800/playSound killAnimal/updateMinigame 9/updateMinigame -1/pause 800/message \"Xarth is defeated, and the Solarion Staff glows peacefully. Order has been restored to the world. / 萨尔斯被击败了，索拉里昂法杖散发着柔和的光芒。世界恢复了秩序！\"/pause 1000/playSound getNewSpecialItem/addMailReceived savedFriends/updateMinigame -2/switchEvent end",
        "sewer": "updateMinigame 4/resetVariable/playMusic pool_ambient/pause 1600/message \"You find yourself in a sewer-like corridor. To your left, a hallway glows with a peculiar green light. To your right, a staircase leads up into the dark. / 你发现自己身处一个类似下水道的地方。左手边，一条通道散发着奇异的绿色光芒。右手边，一段楼梯升入黑暗之中。\"/pause 500/question fork1 \"What do you do?#Enter the hallway to your left.#Climb the stairs to your right. / 你要怎么办？#进入左侧的通道。#登上右侧的楼梯。\"/fork wizardDoor/switchEvent podRoom",
        "swungWeapons": "pause 300/message \"The skeleton is too quick, and strikes out at your party before anyone has a chance to attack! / 骷髅的行动太快，你的队友们还没来得及发动进攻，就已经中招了！\"/playSound killAnimal/updateMinigame -1/pause 1000/message \"The force of the blow sends your party flying backwards. Unable to stop in time, you tumble down a steep slope and splash into something wet. / 巨大的力量将你和你的同伴向后抛去。你们立足不稳，滚下了一道陡峭的斜坡，掉进了一个湿乎乎的地方。\"/pause 100/playSound dropItemInWater/pause 700/switchEvent sewer",
        "healedSam": "playSound healSound/pause 500/speak Sam \"Thanks, @. / 非常感谢，@。\"/speak Sebastian \"...$s / ……$s\"/pause 1000/playMusic none/message \"Sam charges ahead and strikes down Xarth, freeing the Solarion Staff from his clutches and restoring peace and order to the world. / 山姆冲上去砍倒了萨尔斯，将索拉里昂法杖从他手中夺回，和平与秩序重返人间。\"/pause 500/playSound swordswipe/pause 400/playSound killAnimal/updateMinigame 9/updateMinigame -1/pause 1000/playSound getNewSpecialItem/updateMinigame -2/switchEvent end",
        "healer": "pause 500/speak Sebastian \"Healer, huh? That's a very important role.$7 / 牧师吗？那可是个很重要的角色啊。$7#$b#I guess I'll pick the wizard, then. / 那我就选法师好了。\"/speak Sam \"Cool. Warrior's my favorite anyway. / 好啊。反正我最喜欢战士了。\"/addMailReceived choseHealer/switchEvent opening",
        "podRoom": "pause 500/updateMinigame 7/resetVariable/playMusic Hospital_Ambient/pause 1600/message \"You are in a room. On your left is a ladder. On your right, three prisoners are floating in strange, glowing capsules. They appear to be in the process of some kind of transformation. / 你站在一个房间里。左手边有一架梯子。右手边有三个囚犯悬浮在诡异的发光容器里。他们似乎正在接受某种改造。\"/pause 500/message \"Could this be some sick experiment of the Dreadlord's? / 这难道就是恐怖领主的邪恶实验吗？\"/pause 500/question fork0 \"What do you do?#Leave as quickly as possible.#Destroy the capsules. / 你要怎么办？#尽快离开。#摧毁容器。\"/fork leave/pause 500/pause 500/playSound swordswipe/pause 200/playSound breakingGlass/updateMinigame -1/pause 1000/message \"After putting these poor souls to rest, you and your companions climb the ladder. / 在让这些可怜的灵魂安息之后，你和同伴爬上了梯子。\"/pause 800/addMailReceived destroyedPods/playSound woodyStep/pause 400/playSound woodyStep/pause 400/playSound woodyStep/pause 500/switchEvent wizardDoor",
        "decor": "pause 500/stopAnimation Sebastian/speak Sebastian \"Decorations?... Oh, yeah... thanks. I've been sticking posters on the wall for years, I guess it's kinda cluttered. / 装饰？哦，对哦……谢谢了。我在墙上贴海报已经贴好多年了。确实有点乱呢。\"/switchEvent enterRobin",
        "backEntrance": "pause 300/playSound leafrustle/pause 500/playSound grassyStep/pause 400/playSound leafrustle/pause 500/updateMinigame 2/pause 600/message \"After searching around the base of the tower, you discover a trapdoor hidden in the brush. Beneath is a ladder, which your party descends. / 在塔基附近搜索了一番之后，你在灌木丛中发现了一道木板暗门。下面是一架梯子，你和同伴走了下去。\"/pause 800/playSound woodyStep/pause 400/playSound woodyStep/pause 400/playSound woodyStep/pause 500/switchEvent sewer",
        "wizardDoor": "pause 500/updateMinigame 8/resetVariable/playMusic Lava_Ambient/pause 1600/message \"You've come to a door at the end of a hallway. / 在通道尽头，一扇门出现在你们面前。\"/pause 800/message \"The time has come to face Dreadlord Xarth. / 是时候面对恐怖领主萨尔斯了。\"/pause 500/playSound openChest/pause 1000/switchEvent Necromancer",
        "Necromancer": "pause 500/updateMinigame 6/resetVariable/playMusic Lava_Ambient/pause 1600/message \"Xarth: Intruders? How dare you trespass in my private chambers! / 萨尔斯：入侵者？你们竟敢闯入我的住所！\"/pause 800/message \"Ah, so you've come for the Solarion Staff... / 啊，原来你们是为了索拉里昂法杖而来……\"/pause 800/message \"Hehehe... fools. You'll make a nice addition to my skeleton army! / 嘿嘿嘿……真是愚蠢。你们很快就会加入我的骷髅大军！\"/pause 500/fork choseWizard finalBossWizard/fork choseWarrior finalBossWarrior/message \"Dreadlord Xarth casts shadow beam! / 恐怖领主萨尔斯射出暗影光线！\"/pause 500/playSound flameSpell/pause 800/playSound flameSpellHit/updateMinigame -1/pause 1000/message \"You were able to dodge the spell, but your companions are gravely injured! / 你躲开了法术，但你的同伴却受了重伤！\"/pause 500/question fork0 \"What do you do?#Heal the Warrior (Sam).#Heal the Wizard (Sebastian). / 你要怎么办？#治疗战士（山姆）。#治疗法师（塞巴斯蒂安）。\"/pause 500/fork healedSam/playSound healSound/pause 500/speak Sebastian \"Thanks, @.$7 / 非常感谢，@。$7\"/speak Sam \"...$s / ……$s\"/pause 1000/playMusic none/message \"Sebastian casts 'Pure Bolt'... A beam of white light hits Xarth square in the face. The Dreadlord shrieks and crumbles into dust. / 塞巴斯蒂安放出“净化之箭”……一道白光径直击中了萨尔斯的脸。恐怖领主尖叫着化为了灰烬。\"/playSound debuffSpell/pause 500/playSound killAnimal/updateMinigame 9/updateMinigame -1/pause 800/message \"You pick up the Solarion Staff and hold it high. Order has been restored to the world. / 你捡起了索拉里昂法杖，将其高高举起，世界恢复了秩序！\"/addMailReceived savedFriends/pause 1000/playSound getNewSpecialItem/updateMinigame -2/switchEvent end",
        "enterRobin": "pause 500/playSound mouseClick/pause 100/playSound mouseClick/pause 500/playSound Pickup_Coin15/pause 300/emote Sebastian 40/speak Sebastian \"That was an instant message from Sam... I guess he wants to hang out... / 是山姆的短信……看来他是想找我出去玩……#$b#Ugh, I don't really feel like going out today.$u / 呃，我今天不太想出门。$u\"/pause 500/playSound doorClose/warp Robin 1 1/move Robin 0 4 1/speak Robin \"Oh, hi @. / 啊，你好！@。\"/faceDirection farmer 3/move Robin 4 0 1/speak Robin \"Sebby, I know you don't like it when I come in here... but I ran into Abigail at the store and she said she was looking for you. / 我知道你不想让我进来……但我今天遇到了阿比盖尔，她说她在找你。\"/pause 200/emote Sebastian 28/speak Sebastian \"Did you tell her I'm working? / 你有没有和她说我在工作？\"/speak Robin \"I did... but she said she'd probably stop by anyway. / 说了……不过她说她可能还是要来。\"/emote Sebastian 12/speak Sebastian \"*sigh*... No one takes my job seriously.$u / *唉*……大家都不把我的工作当回事儿。$u#$b#No one ever bothers Maru when she's working at the clinic... does everyone think I'm just surfing the web all day? / 玛鲁在诊所工作的时候就没人去打扰她……难道大家以为我整天就是在网上闲逛吗？\"/faceDirection farmer 0 true/move Robin -4 0 0/move Robin 0 -4 0/warp Robin -100 -100/playSound doorClose/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 0/resetVariable/question fork1 \"#Ask him about his career goals.#Ask him why he doesn't want to see his friends. / #问问他的工作目标。#问问他为什么不想见到朋友。\"/fork noFriends/pause 500/speak Sebastian \"Well, I'm trying to save up so I can move out of here. Probably to the city or something. / 嗯，我是想攒钱搬家。搬到城里什么的。\"/emote Sebastian 40/speak Sebastian \"You know, if I'd gone to college I'd probably be making six figures right now... but I just don't want to be part of that corporate rat race, you know? / 我要是上了大学，现在怎么也赚到六位数了……但我并不想进入企业，过什么勾心斗角的日子，你懂吧？#$b#Well, and I guess I just feel more comfortable hidden behind the computer than dealing with people face-to-face.$s / 看来，与其让我和人面对面相处，还是躲藏在屏幕后面要舒服得多啊。$s\"/emote Sebastian 28/pause 600/playSound mouseClick/pause 100/playSound mouseClick/pause 300/speak Sebastian \"Well, I should get back to work... I need to get this module finished by tomorrow. / 我得继续工作了……明天之前要把这个模块完成才行。\"/animate Sebastian false true 100 24 24 24 24 24 24 24 24 24 24 25 26 27 26 27 26 27 26 25 24 24/playSound keyboardTyping/pause 500/move farmer 0 2 3/move farmer -3 0 0/move farmer 0 -2 3/move farmer -5 0 0 true/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 1000/end",
        "leave": "pause 500/message \"Putting the disturbing sight of the prisoners out of your mind, you and your companions quickly climb the ladder. / 将可怕的囚徒影像抛诸脑后，你和同伴飞快地爬上了梯子。\"/pause 800/playSound woodyStep/pause 400/playSound woodyStep/pause 400/playSound woodyStep/pause 500/switchEvent wizardDoor",
        "didntLeave": "pause 5500/stopAnimation Sebastian/speak Sebastian \"Okay. Sorry about that, I just needed to finish what I was working on. / 好吧。真是抱歉，我要先把手头的事情搞定。\"/switchEvent sebastianRoom",
        "ranAway": "pause 300/message \"You turn and run along a dim corridor. The cold stone slopes and spirals downward for what seems like an eternity. Finally, you emerge into a new area. / 你沿着昏暗的走廊左绕右转。冰冷的石头旋转着向下延伸，仿佛无穷无尽。终于，你进入了一片新的区域。\"/pause 400/switchEvent sewer",
        "sebastianRoom": "resetVariable/move farmer 0 2 1/playSound mouseClick/move farmer 3 0 0/playSound mouseClick/move farmer 0 -1 0/playSound mouseClick/move farmer 0 -1 0/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 0/question fork1 \"#Ask him what he's working on.#Compliment the decor in his room. / #问问他刚刚在干什么。#称赞他房间的装饰。\"/fork decor/pause 500/stopAnimation Sebastian/speak Sebastian \"I do freelance work as a programmer. / 我有时候会接一些编程的零活。\"/switchEvent enterRobin",
        "opening": "pause 500/speak Sebastian \"Let's begin... / 我们开始吧……\"/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/playMusic Crystal Bells/cutscene boardGame/pause 1700/message \"The King has entrusted you and your companions with recovering the Solarion Staff... a task which, if completed successfully, will ensure your place in the hall of legends as well as a sizable fortune of gold and silver. / 国王派你和你的同伴前去取回索拉里昂法杖……如果能够成功，你们的大名将流芳百世，还会获得数不完花不尽的金银财宝。\"/pause 800/message \"After a long month journeying across unforgiving lands, you step out onto a precipice to see your destination looming in the distance. / 经过一个月的长途跋涉后，你登上了一座悬崖，隐约发现你的目标就坐落在前方。\"/pause 100/message \"There, beyond a moonlit plain, lies the Necromancer's Tower... where Dreadlord Xarth usurps the power of the stolen Solarion Staff for his vile purposes. / 在那月光照耀的平原对面，就是死灵法师塔……在塔里，恐怖领主萨尔斯正从他偷来的索拉里昂法杖中汲取能量，以实现自己邪恶的计划。\"/pause 500/pause 700/updateMinigame 1/resetVariable/pause 700/question fork1 \"The tower lies before you.#Go in the front. Fortune favors the bold.#Search for a back entrance. Let's remain hidden. / 塔就矗立在你的面前。#从正门进入。不入虎穴焉得虎子。#寻找后门，以免打草惊蛇。\"/fork backEntrance/pause 500/updateMinigame 3/pause 50/playSound skeletonStep/pause 100/playMusic bigDrums/pause 500/message \"A skeleton guards the hallway before you. It looks dangerous. / 一个骷髅拦住了你的去路。它似乎很难对付。\"/pause 900/resetVariable/question fork1 \"What do you do?#Fight the skeleton.#Run away. / 你要怎么办？#与骷髅对战。#逃跑。\"/fork ranAway/pause 500/resetVariable/question fork0 \"The skeleton lunges forward!#Swing your weapons.#Raise your shields. / 骷髅冲了过来！#挥动武器。#举起盾牌。\"/fork swungWeapons/pause 600/playSound clubhit/updateMinigame -1/pause 500/message \"You successfully block the attack. The skeleton stumbles backward, giving you enough time to strike out and slay the foul creature. / 你成功挡下了攻击。骷髅向后倒退了几步，你趁机冲上去，一击了结了这可怕的生物。\"/pause 200/playSound swordswipe/pause 400/playSound skeletonDie/updateMinigame 5/updateMinigame -1/pause 1000/addMailReceived killedSkeleton/message \"You continue down the hallway, taking care not to step on the skeleton's remains. / 你小心翼翼地绕开骷髅的遗骸，沿着过道继续前进。\"/pause 900/switchEvent sewer",
        "2794460/f Sebastian 500/p Sebastian": "Hospital_Ambient/-1000 -1000/farmer 1 1 2 Sebastian 9 4 3 Robin -100 -100 2/skippable/doAction 1 3/removeTile 1 3 Buildings/removeTile 1 2 Front/playSound keyboardTyping/showFrame Sebastian 24/animate Sebastian false true 100 26 27 26 27 26 27 26/viewport 6 6 true/move farmer 0 4 1/move farmer 5 0 1/pause 1000/speak Sebastian \"Oh, hey. Gimme one sec. / 哦，嗨。稍等一下。\"/pause 500/playSound keyboardTyping/pause 1000/question fork1 \"#He's busy... I should leave.#Stay put. / #他很忙……我还是走吧。#待在原地。\"/fork didntLeave/move farmer -2 0 3/speak Sebastian \"Where are you going?$u / 你要去哪儿？$u\"/pause 300/faceDirection farmer 1/stopAnimation Sebastian/speak Sebastian \"Sorry... I had to finish this line before I lost my train of thought. / 抱歉……我得在思路被打断之前，把这一行搞定。\"/pause 500/move farmer 2 0 1/switchEvent sebastianRoom",
        "end": "playMusic Hospital_Ambient/pause 9000/viewport 5 5 true/pause 800/showFrame Sebastian 29/speak Sebastian \"Hey, not bad!$7 / 嘿，不错！$7#$b#It took me like, three or four tries to beat my first scenario.$7 / 我用了三四回才通过第一幕呢。$7\"/emote farmer 32/pause 1000/speak Sebastian \"Thanks for stopping by... I'll see you later.$7 / 多谢拜访……回头见啦。$7\"/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 1000/end"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Events/SeedShop",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "16/f Pierre 1500/p Pierre": "Hospital_Ambient/20 5/farmer 20 12 0 Pierre 14 15 0/skippable/doAction 20 11/move farmer 0 -7 1/move farmer -1 0 0/move farmer 0 -1 0/pause 600/faceDirection farmer 1/pause 1000/showFrame 35/emote farmer 8/pause 1000/playSound secret1/stopAnimation farmer/message \"Found Pierre's 'secret stash'. / 你找到了皮埃尔的“秘密收藏”。\"/pause 1000/speak Pierre \"Hey! Who's in the bedroom?$4 / 嘿！谁在卧室里？$4\"/warp Pierre 20 12 true/faceDirection Pierre 0/playMusic ragtime/move Pierre 0 -4 0 true/faceDirection farmer 2 true/showFrame 94/jump farmer/pause 1000/stopAnimation farmer/proceedPosition Pierre/emote Pierre 16/speed Pierre 4/move Pierre 0 -3 1 false/move Pierre -1 0 0/faceDirection farmer 2/speak Pierre \"Wha...? How did you find that?!$4 / 你……你是怎么发现的？！$4\"/faceDirection Pierre 2/pause 200/faceDirection Pierre 0/speak Pierre \"Quick, give it to me!$u / 快给我！$u\"/showFrame 95/pause 300/playSound coin/pause 600/showFrame 0/pause 500/speak Pierre \"$q 50 null#Promise me you won't tell anyone about this. / 发誓你不会把这事儿告诉任何人。#$r 50 70 Event_naga1#Your secret is safe with me. / 我会为你保守秘密的。#$r 50 -500 Event_naga2#Your wife deserves to know about this. / 这事儿应该让你太太知道。\"/pause 500/speed Pierre 2/move Pierre 1 0 2/emote Pierre 12/speak Pierre \"*grumble*...now I have to find a new hiding spot...*grumble*$u  / *嘟囔*……这下又得找个新的藏匿点了……*嘟囔*$u\"/move Pierre 0 8 0 true/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/end",
        "3/f Abigail 2000/p Abigail/t 2000 2200/n abbySpiritBoard": "echos/-1000 -1000/farmer 13 6 3 Abigail 6 8 1/skippable/specificTemporarySprite abbyOuijaCandles/viewport 7 5/speak Abigail \"Hey! I was hoping you'd show up. I wanna show you something. / 嘿！我正想着你什么时候来呢。我想给你看一样东西。\"/move farmer -5 0 0/move farmer 0 2 3/faceDirection Abigail 2/speak Abigail \"See this? It's called a spirit board. Have you ever used one? / 你看到了吗？这个就是通灵板。你以前用过吗？\"/emote farmer 8/move Abigail 0 2 1/move farmer 0 2 3/pause 500/speak Abigail \"Put your hands on the planchette with me...$l / 把咱俩的手一起放到板子上……$l\"/showFrame Abigail 30/pause 200/animate farmer true true 9999 89/pause 600/speak Abigail \"Now the spirits will guide us toward a...$h / 现在，灵魂将把我们领向……$h\"/showFrame Abigail 31/pause 500/speak Abigail \"LOOK, it's moving!$7 / 快看！在动诶！$7\"/emote farmer 16/speak Abigail \"The first letter is... 'I' ... / 第一个字母是……“我” ……\"/pause 600/speak Abigail \"Next is... '<' ... / 下一个是……“<”……\"/pause 800/speak Abigail \"Wow, look at it go! It's spelling out... '%firstnameletter'... / 哇，快看它动的多带劲！它写着……“%firstnameletter”……#$b#I < %firstnameletter...? / 我 < %firstnameletter……？\"/emote Abigail 16/showFrame Abigail 12/faceDirection Abigail 3/stopMusic/pause 200/stopAnimation farmer/faceDirection Abigail 1/pause 400/specificTemporarySprite abbyOuija/playSound swordswipe/pause 900/playSound seeds/pause 500/speak Abigail \"Oops, accidentally knocked over the board! Heh heh...$h / 哎呀，一不留神把板子打翻了！嘻嘻……$h#$b#It's just a silly game, it doesn't mean anything.$9 / 这就是个蠢游戏，没什么意义的啦。$9\"/faceDirection Abigail 3/emote Abigail 60/faceDirection Abigail 1/speak Abigail \"I, um, have something to do. You'll have to go... Sorry.$9 / 我，呃，还有事要做。你得走了……对不起了。$9\"/faceDirection Abigail 2/emote farmer 28/pause 500/move farmer 0 -3 0/pause 800/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 1000/move farmer 5 0 1 true/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/end invisibleWarpOut Abigail",
        "3102768/j 15/H": "playful/6 21/farmer 6 29 0 Pierre 4 17 2 Gus 9 26 1 Marnie 3 23 0 Jodi 11 20 0 Demetrius 9 17 3 Morris -100 -100 0/broadcastEvent/skippable/move farmer 0 -5 0/move Gus 0 1 1 true/move Jodi -1 0 0 true/move farmer 0 -5 0 false/pause 500/move Pierre 1 0 2/speak Pierre \"Welcome To Pierre's! How can I help you? / 欢迎来到皮埃尔商店！有什么需要的吗？\"/pause 1000/playSound doorClose/warp Morris 6 29/pause 1000/emote Pierre 8/playSound dwop/faceDirection farmer 1 true/pause 50/faceDirection farmer 2/move Morris 0 -2 0/move Morris 0 -5 0/speak Morris \"Ahem... / 那个……\"/pause 1000/faceDirection Marnie 1/faceDirection Gus 0/pause 1000/move Morris 1 0 1/speak Morris \"Come and get it folks... coupons for 50% off your purchase at JojaMart! / 大家快来哦……Joja 超市五折优惠券大派送啦！\"/jump Pierre/textAboveHead Pierre \"50 Percent!?!? / 五折？！？！\"/showFrame Pierre 16/shake Pierre 3000/faceDirection Demetrius 2/faceDirection Jodi 3/pause 1000/animate Morris false true 80 16 17 16 18/pause 1000/showFrame Pierre 0/speak Morris \"Well? Any takers? / 嗯？有没有人要啊？\"/pause 500/advancedMove Marnie false 4 0/advancedMove Gus false -2 0 0 -3 -1 0 0 -2/advancedMove Jodi false -3 0 0 1/advancedMove Demetrius false 0 5 -1 0/pause 1500/globalFade/viewport -1000 1000/playMusic none/pause 500/warp Marnie -100 -100/warp Demetrius -100 -100/warp Jodi -100 -100/warp Gus -100 -100/playSound doorClose/pause 1000/playSound doorClose/pause 1000/playSound doorClose/pause 500/playSound doorClose/pause 1000/speak Pierre \"But... I can't match those prices! I'd be selling at a loss!$s / 但……这价格我可比不了啊！这简直是赔本贱卖！$s\"/stopAnimation Morris/viewport 6 18 true/move Morris 0 -3 0/faceDirection farmer 1/pause 1000/speak Morris \"It must be so difficult for you... To lose your loyal customers like that. / 失去了这么忠实的顾客……一定很难受吧。#$b#But can you blame them? Joja Corporation is clearly the superior choice.$h / 但怎么能怪他们呢？显然，Joja 企业才是正确的选择。$h#$b#Soon the whole town will realize that. / 很快，全镇的人都会意识到这一点。\"/faceDirection farmer 1/emote Pierre 28/playSound dwop/faceDirection Morris 3 true/pause 50/faceDirection Morris 2/move Morris 0 10 2 true/pause 1000/faceDirection farmer 2 true/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/end dialogue Pierre \"Sigh...$s\"",
        "beatGame": "playMusic jaunty/speak Abigail \"Hey, that was fun!$h / 嘿，挺有意思的！$h#$b#Well thanks, @. You seem to really know your way around a joystick, huh? I guess that makes sense. $h / 好的，谢谢。@，你用手柄还真是有一套啊。这倒也说得通。$h^Thanks, @. I didn't think you'd know how to work a joystick so well! But it seems you're experienced.$h / 非常感谢。@。本没想到你玩操作杆这么娴熟！感觉像是很有经验的样子呢！$h\"/pause 500/emote Abigail 32/pause 1000/end",
        "963113/n pierreQualityCrops": "distantBanjo/5 19/farmer 5 23 0 Pierre 5 17 2 Gus 5 19 0 Jodi 5 21 0 Marnie 10 20 0 Robin 2 24 3 Evelyn 9 26 1/hostMail MSB_Pierre/skippable/pause 3000/speak Pierre \"Gus, I have just the thing for you... / 格斯，我这里正有你想要的东西……\"/speak Gus \"I'm all ears. / 愿闻其详。\"/speak Pierre \"It's a bundle of locally sourced, organic, heirloom veggies... / 是一袋原种的有机蔬菜，本地生产的……#$b#These are hand picked and sorted, to ensure only the very finest in quality and taste. / 经过精挑细选，质量和味道上乘。#$b#This is a once-in-a-lifetime kind of offer! / 过了这个村，就没这店了！\"/speak Gus \"That sounds pretty good! I could use some quality veggies for the saloon. How much does it cost? / 听起来不错嘛！我在餐吧里用得到优质蔬菜。多少钱？\"/jump Pierre/pause 800/speak Pierre \"ONLY... *mumble* mumble* / 只！要！……（咕哝咕哝）\"/emote Gus 8/speak Gus \"What was that? / 什么玩意？#$b#Hahaha... for a moment there, I thought I heard, '25,000g'.$h / 哈哈哈……我还以为我听到了“25,000 金”。$h\"/emote Pierre 40/speak Pierre \"Heh... that's right. It really is a bargain, isn't it? / 呃……就是这个价。确实很便宜吧？\"/jump Gus/shake Gus 1000/pause 1000/speak Gus \"Pierre, are you crazy? There's no way I could afford that. I'd have to sell the saloon!$3 / 皮埃尔，你疯了吗？我压根买不起，除非我把餐吧卖了！$3\"/advancedMove Gus false 3 0 4 9999/move Jodi 0 -2 0 true/move farmer 0 -2 0 false/speak Jodi \"I overheard the price... that's outrageous! You should be ashamed.$3 / 我无意中听到了价格……太离谱了！你应该感到惭愧。$3\"/move Jodi 1 0 1/speak Pierre \"Wait! How about 10,000g then!?$4 / 等等！10,000 金如何？！$4\"/textAboveHead Jodi \"No way! / 不可能！\"/move Jodi 1 0 1/faceDirection Gus 3/pause 1000/emote Pierre 28/pause 100/proceedPosition Jodi/move farmer 0 -1 0/pause 500/speak Pierre \"It's a disaster, @... $s / 太糟糕了，@……$s#$b#I thought this was a surefire business strategy.$s / 我以为这个做生意的策略特别靠谱。$s#$b#But it turns out, no one is willing to buy vegetables at a 10x price markup, even if I put the little 'organic' sticker on them.$s / 结果发现，即使我贴了个“有机”的标签，还是没有人愿意以 10 倍的差价买蔬菜。$s\"/pause 400/quickQuestion #You win some, you lose some#You should be less greedy#I'm offended they didn't want my veggies(break)pause 300\\speak Pierre \"You're right, you can't run a business without taking some risk. / 你说得对，做生意总会有风险。\"(break)emote Pierre 12\\speak Pierre \"Hey, I'm not forcing anyone to buy it! If they don't like the price, they can move on.$3\"\\pause 1000\\speak Pierre \"...But, I guess you have a point. If I make all my customers angry, then pretty soon I won't have any customers at all...$s\"(break)faceDirection Jodi 3\\speak Jodi \"Your veggies look great, @. It's Pierre's price that turned us away.\"\\faceDirection Jodi 1\\pause 1000/emote Pierre 40/speak Pierre \"By the way, @... you look like you could really use a veggie dinner tonight. / @，说起来……说不定你今天可以用这个蔬菜做一顿晚餐。#$b#What do you say, wanna buy these back for the low, low price of 2,501g? / 你觉得呢，想要以 2,501 金的抄底价买回去吗？\"/emote farmer 12/end",
        "17/f Caroline 1500/p Caroline/p Abigail": "50s/35 9/farmer 31 13 0 Abigail 34 9 1 Caroline 35 9 3/skippable/move farmer 0 -1 0/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 0/speak Abigail \"Stop telling me how to live my life!$a / 不要再对我的生活指手画脚了！$a\"/pause 500/speak Caroline \"Hey, cut it out! We're letting you live here free of charge until you finish school. It seems like you don't appreciate that at all!$u / 喂，别闹了！我们让你在读完书之前住在这里，一个钱都不花。但看样子你一点感激的意思都没有啊！$u\"/emote Abigail 12/speak Abigail \"Stop trying to make me feel guilty.$a / 不要再让我内疚了。$a#$b#I appreciate that you and Dad are helping me out, but expecting me to dress the way you want is ridiculous.$a / 有你和老爸帮忙，我真的很感激，但让我按照你们的方式生活，实在是太不可理喻了。$a#$b#I'm not a little girl anymore, Mom.$u / 我已经不是小姑娘了，妈。$u\"/faceDirection Caroline 1/pause 1500/faceDirection Caroline 3/speak Caroline \"...You're right. I'm sorry.$s / ……你说得对。我很抱歉。$s\"/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 2/playSound woodyStep/faceDirection Abigail 2 true/faceDirection Caroline 2/speak Abigail \"Is someone there?$7 / 有人在吗？$7\"/faceDirection farmer 0/speed farmer 4/move farmer 0 1 3/speed farmer 4/move farmer -4 0 2 true/move Abigail -3 0 2 false/emote Abigail 8/speak Abigail \"I swear, this house is haunted. / 我和你说，这屋子绝对在闹鬼。\"/emote Caroline 40/pause 500/end dialogue Abigail \"Urgghh...$a#$b#Sorry... I was fighting with my Mom earlier.$s\"",
        "1/f Abigail 500/p Abigail/d Sat": "none/-9999 -4/farmer 13 6 3 Abigail 3 6 2/skippable/showFrame Abigail 20/specificTemporarySprite abbyvideoscreen/viewport 9 4 true/pause 1000/playSound Cowboy_gunshot/pause 150/emote Abigail 52/pause 800/playSound Cowboy_gunshot/pause 150/playSound Cowboy_gunshot/pause 150/playSound Cowboy_gunshot/temporarySprite 2 4 27 8 50/shake Abigail 500/pause 150/playSound Cowboy_gunshot/pause 150/temporarySprite 4 4 27 8 50 true/playSound Cowboy_gunshot/pause 450/playSound Cowboy_monsterDie/pause 550/playSound Cowboy_gunshot/pause 150/playSound cowboy_dead/pause 850/emote Abigail 28/playMusic distantBanjo/showFrame Abigail 21/pause 80/showFrame Abigail 22/pause 80/move farmer -1 0 3/move farmer -3 0 3/faceDirection Abigail 1/pause 200/emote Abigail 16/pause 600/speak Abigail \"@? / @？\"/move farmer -3 0 3/speak Abigail \"You scared me, sneaking into my room like that! / 你怎么偷偷溜进我的房间，吓死我了！\"/faceDirection Abigail 0/speak Abigail \"*sigh*... so I've been playing 'Journey of the Prairie King' for hours and I can't even beat the first level...$s / *唉*……我玩“草原之王的冒险之旅”已经好几个小时了，却连第一关都过不去……$s#$b#This game is ridiculously hard!$a / 这游戏难度也太夸张了吧！$a#$b#Well, either that or I'm just terrible at it.$s / 呃，要不然就是我技术太差了。$s\"/faceDirection Abigail 1/pause 1000/emote Abigail 16/pause 300/speak Abigail \"Hey, do you want to try this level together with me? I think I might do better with your help. / 嘿，你要不要和我一起玩玩这一关？有你帮忙应该会简单些。\"/faceDirection farmer 3/farmerAnimation 97/pause 1000/faceDirection Abigail 0/move farmer 0 1 3/move farmer -4 0 0/move farmer 0 -1 0/faceDirection farmer 0/pause 500/globalFade/cutscene AbigailGame/pause 500/faceDirection Abigail 3/stopMusic/faceDirection farmer 1/fork beatGame/pause 600/emote Abigail 28/pause 400/speak Abigail \"Ugh, I give up... I'll never get past the first level.$s / 呃，我放弃了……看来这辈子是过不了第二关了。$s#$b#Oh well... thanks for trying. / 好吧……至少努力过了。\"/faceDirection farmer 2/showFrame 96/emote farmer 40/pause 1000/end",
        "58/f Harvey 1500/t 1100 1500": "aerobics/-1000 -1000/farmer 14 12 1 Harvey 23 20 0 Marnie 23 18 0 Emily 23 16 0 Robin 25 18 0 Pam 25 16 0 Caroline 24 14 2 Jodi 27 16 0 Leah 27 18 0/skippable/showFrame Harvey 26/viewport 24 17 true/pause 500/faceDirection Caroline 3 true/pause 500/screenFlash 1/showFrame Harvey 27 true/faceDirection Marnie 3 true/faceDirection Leah 3 true/faceDirection Jodi 3 true/faceDirection Pam 3 true/faceDirection Robin 3 true/faceDirection Emily 3 true/pause 500/faceDirection Leah 1 true/faceDirection Jodi 1 true/faceDirection Caroline 1/pause 500/showFrame Harvey 25 true/faceDirection Marnie 1 true/faceDirection Pam 1 true/faceDirection Robin 1 true/faceDirection Emily 1 true/pause 500/faceDirection Caroline 2/pause 500/faceDirection Leah 0 true/faceDirection Jodi 0 true/faceDirection Marnie 0 true/faceDirection Pam 0 true/faceDirection Robin 0 true/faceDirection Emily 0 true/pause 300/showFrame Harvey 26 true/pause 200/pause 500/faceDirection Caroline 3 true/pause 500/faceDirection Leah 3 true/faceDirection Jodi 3 true/faceDirection Marnie 3 true/faceDirection Pam 3 true/faceDirection Robin 3 true/faceDirection Emily 3 true/pause 350/showFrame Harvey 27 true/pause 150/faceDirection Caroline 1/pause 500/faceDirection Leah 1 true/faceDirection Jodi 1 true/showFrame Harvey 25 true/faceDirection Marnie 1 true/faceDirection Pam 1 true/faceDirection Robin 1 true/faceDirection Emily 1 true/pause 500/faceDirection Caroline 2/pause 500/faceDirection Leah 0 true/faceDirection Jodi 0 true/faceDirection Marnie 0 true/faceDirection Pam 0 true/faceDirection Robin 0 true/faceDirection Emily 0 true/showFrame Harvey 26 true/pause 500/faceDirection Marnie 0 true/faceDirection Pam 0 true/faceDirection Robin 0 true/faceDirection Emily 0 true/showFrame Harvey 26 true/faceDirection Caroline 0 true/pause 1000/faceDirection Leah 1 true/faceDirection Jodi 1 true/faceDirection Marnie 1 true/faceDirection Pam 1 true/faceDirection Robin 1 true/faceDirection Emily 1 true/showFrame Harvey 25 true/faceDirection Caroline 1 true/pause 1000/faceDirection Leah 2 true/faceDirection Jodi 2 true/faceDirection Marnie 2 true/faceDirection Pam 2 true/faceDirection Robin 2 true/faceDirection Emily 2 true/showFrame Harvey 24 true/faceDirection Caroline 2 true/pause 1000/faceDirection Leah 3 true/faceDirection Jodi 3 true/faceDirection Marnie 3 true/faceDirection Pam 3 true/faceDirection Robin 3 true/faceDirection Emily 3 true/showFrame Harvey 27 true/faceDirection Caroline 3 true/pause 1000/faceDirection Leah 0 true/faceDirection Jodi 0 true/faceDirection Marnie 0 true/faceDirection Pam 0 true/faceDirection Robin 0 true/faceDirection Emily 0 true/showFrame Harvey 26 true/faceDirection Caroline 0 true/pause 500/faceDirection Marnie 0 true/faceDirection Pam 0 true/faceDirection Robin 0 true/faceDirection Emily 0 true/showFrame Harvey 26 true/faceDirection Caroline 0 true/pause 1000/faceDirection Leah 1 true/faceDirection Jodi 1 true/faceDirection Marnie 1 true/faceDirection Pam 1 true/faceDirection Robin 1 true/faceDirection Emily 1 true/showFrame Harvey 25 true/faceDirection Caroline 1 true/pause 1000/faceDirection Leah 2 true/faceDirection Jodi 2 true/faceDirection Marnie 2 true/faceDirection Pam 2 true/faceDirection Robin 2 true/faceDirection Emily 2 true/showFrame Harvey 24 true/faceDirection Caroline 2 true/pause 1000/faceDirection Leah 3 true/faceDirection Jodi 3 true/faceDirection Marnie 3 true/faceDirection Pam 3 true/faceDirection Robin 3 true/faceDirection Emily 3 true/showFrame Harvey 27 true/faceDirection Caroline 3 true/pause 1000/faceDirection Leah 0 true/faceDirection Jodi 0 true/faceDirection Marnie 0 true/faceDirection Pam 0 true/faceDirection Robin 0 true/faceDirection Emily 0 true/showFrame Harvey 26 true/faceDirection Caroline 2 true/screenFlash 1/pause 2000/speak Caroline \"Alright! That concludes our aerobics class! / 好吧。好，今天的体操课就到此为止！#$b#Are you breaking a sweat?$h / 你出汗了没？$h\"/pause 500/speak Harvey \"*pant*...*pant*...Yes.$7 / *喘息*……*喘息*……出了。$7\"/move Pam -1 0 3 true/faceDirection Jodi 2/faceDirection Emily 1 true/viewport move 0 -1 3000/move farmer 3 0 1/faceDirection Robin 3/faceDirection Marnie 1 true/move Harvey -3 0 0/move Harvey 0 -8 3/emote Harvey 16/speak Harvey \"@! You were watching me?$8 / @！你一直在看吗？$8#$b#...How embarrassing... I didn't want anyone to know. Least of all you.$s / ……真是丢人……本来还想瞒着大家呢。至少也不该让你知道。$s\"/move Harvey -2 0 3/speak Harvey \"I'm just trying to stay healthy. As you get older, it requires more effort. / 我只是想保持健康的体魄。毕竟年纪大了，就更需要努力了。#$b#I'm not in very good shape, though... I can hardly keep up with them.$s / 但我身体还是不行……总觉得跟不上他们呢。$s\"/pause 400/faceDirection Harvey 1/faceDirection Harvey 3/speak Harvey \"$q -1 null#Look... Don't tell everyone in town that I'm doing dance aerobics, okay? / 听着……别告诉镇上的人我在跳健身操，好吗？#$r -1 20 event_aerobics1#I won't tell. / 我不会说的。#$r -1 -50 event_aerobics2#I can't promise that. / 这我可说不好。\"/pause 500/end dialogue Harvey \"Wow, that was quite a workout...\""
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Events/Sewer",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "691039/f Dwarf 50/n CF_Sewer/d Fri": "Overcast/16 13/farmer -1000 -1000 0 Dwarf 14 13 1 Krobus 18 13 3 Wizard -1000 -1000 2/skippable/pause 500/emote Dwarf 12/speak Dwarf \"A Shadow Person, above ground? This is outrageous! / 暗影人，在地面上？太离谱了！#$b#Your people were responsible for the death of my entire family. / 我全族的死都是因为你们。\"/move Krobus -1 0 3/emote Krobus 12/playSound shadowpeep/speak Krobus \"If you dwarves hadn't driven us from our ancestral home, we'd never have had to resort to violence! / 如果你们矮人没把我们从祖祖辈辈居住的家园赶出，我们也不会武力讨伐！#$b#I'm sorry about your family. / 你族人的事我很抱歉。\"/move Dwarf 1 0 1/speak Dwarf \"'Sorry' isn't going to cut it. / 光道歉有什么用。\"/jump Dwarf/pause 500/animate Dwarf false true 50 4 5 6 7/jump Krobus/pause 500/animate Krobus false true 50 12 13 14 15/pause 1000/playSound throw/positionOffset Dwarf 4 0/positionOffset Krobus -4 0/pause 30/positionOffset Dwarf 4 0/positionOffset Krobus -4 0/pause 30/positionOffset Dwarf 4 0/positionOffset Krobus -4 0/pause 30/positionOffset Dwarf 4 0/positionOffset Krobus -4 0/pause 30/positionOffset Dwarf 4 0/positionOffset Krobus -4 0/pause 30/positionOffset Dwarf 4 0/positionOffset Krobus -4 0/pause 30/positionOffset Dwarf 4 0/positionOffset Krobus -4 0/pause 30/positionOffset Dwarf 4 0/positionOffset Krobus -4 0/pause 30/positionOffset Dwarf 4 0/positionOffset Krobus -4 0/pause 30/positionOffset Dwarf 4 0/positionOffset Krobus -4 0/pause 30/positionOffset Dwarf 4 0/positionOffset Krobus -4 0/pause 30/positionOffset Dwarf 4 0/positionOffset Krobus -4 0/pause 30/positionOffset Dwarf 4 0/positionOffset Krobus -4 0/pause 30/positionOffset Dwarf 4 0/positionOffset Krobus -4 0/pause 30/positionOffset Dwarf 4 0/positionOffset Krobus -4 0/pause 30/shake Dwarf 500/playSound clubhit/jump Krobus/pause 500/shake Krobus 500/playSound clubSmash/jump Dwarf/pause 500/shake Dwarf 250/pause 250/playSound hitEnemy/pause 250/shake Krobus 250/playSound shadowHit/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 0 true/animate farmer false true 500 13 14/warp farmer 16 9/playSound stoneStep/shake Dwarf 250/pause 250/playSound hitEnemy/pause 250/playSound stoneStep/positionOffset farmer 0 16/shake Krobus 250/playSound shadowHit/pause 500/playSound stoneStep/positionOffset farmer 0 16/shake Dwarf 250/pause 250/playSound hitEnemy/pause 250/positionOffset farmer 0 16/shake Krobus 250/playSound shadowHit/pause 500/playSound stoneStep/positionOffset farmer 0 16/shake Dwarf 250/pause 250/playSound hitEnemy/pause 250/playSound stoneStep/positionOffset farmer 0 16/shake Krobus 250/playSound shadowHit/pause 500/positionOffset farmer 0 16/shake Dwarf 250/pause 250/playSound hitEnemy/pause 250/playSound stoneStep/positionOffset farmer 0 16/shake Krobus 250/playSound shadowHit/pause 500/playSound stoneStep/positionOffset farmer 0 16/warp farmer 16 11/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 300/showFrame farmer 94/jump farmer/startJittering/pause 1000/stopJittering/speed farmer 6/showFrame 0/move farmer 0 2 2 true/pause 300/shake Dwarf 1000/shake Krobus 1000/playSound clubSmash/positionOffset Dwarf -16 0/positionOffset Krobus 16 0/pause 30/positionOffset Dwarf -16 0/positionOffset Krobus 16 0/pause 30/positionOffset Dwarf -16 0/positionOffset Krobus 16 0/pause 30/positionOffset Dwarf -16 0/positionOffset Krobus 16 0/pause 30/showFrame farmer 0/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 3/faceDirection farmer 1/faceDirection farmer 2/speak Dwarf \"Let me at him! He's despicable. / 让我来教训教训他！他这人太恶心了。\"/speak Krobus \"Come and get it, shrimpy. / 来比划比划啊，小矮子。\"/playMusic none/pause 1000/playSound wand/screenFlash 3/showFrame Wizard 16/warp Wizard 16 16/pause 2000/showFrame Wizard 0/pause 500/faceDirection Wizard 1 true/pause 50/faceDirection Wizard 0/pause 800/showFrame Wizard 17/screenFlash .35/playSound flameSpellHit/shake Wizard 500/specificTemporarySprite wizardSewerMagic/stopAnimation Krobus/stopAnimation Dwarf/faceDirection Krobus 2 true/faceDirection Dwarf 2 true/shake Krobus 1000/shake Dwarf 1000/pause 1000/speak Wizard \"Silence! Both of you! / 都给我闭嘴！你们俩！\"/pause 500/showFrame Wizard 8/playSound dwop/pause 1000/playMusic Upper_Ambient/speak Wizard \"The Elemental Wars have long been finished. You have no reason to be fighting any longer. / 元素战争早就结束了。你们俩已经没有继续战斗的理由了。#$b#The two of you must make peace for the sake of the humans that live around you. Surely you can see that. / 为了在你们周围的人类中生活，你们必须和好才行。这道理你们都懂吧！\"/pause 1000/faceDirection Dwarf 3 true/faceDirection Krobus 1 true/pause 500/emote Dwarf 40 true/emote Krobus 40 true/pause 3000/speak Dwarf \"Very well. I'll stay away from the sewer from now on. / 很好，我以后再也不会靠近下水道了。\"/faceDirection farmer 3/faceDirection Dwarf 1/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 1/pause 500/faceDirection Krobus 3/speak Krobus \"...And I'm truly sorry about the past, Dwarf. I have no personal gripe with you. / ……对于过去的事情我真的很抱歉，矮人。我对你个人并没有什么不满。\"/pause 1000/faceDirection farmer 2 true/faceDirection Dwarf 2 true/faceDirection Krobus 2 true/pause 1000/speak Wizard \"Very good. I shall cast a 'Seal of Promise' to finalize this agreement. / 很好。那就让我用“誓言之印”来达成最终协议吧。\"/pause 1000/faceDirection Wizard 3 true/playSound dwop/pause 50/faceDirection Wizard 2/pause 1500/showFrame Wizard 16/playSound yoba/specificTemporarySprite WizardPromise/pause 3000/speed farmer 2/move farmer 0 -2 2/emote farmer 40/pause 800/end"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Events/Sunroom",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "719926/t 900 1700/w sunny": "spring_day_ambient/-885 8/farmer -500 -500 0 Caroline 5 7 1/mail CarolineTea/skippable/specificTemporarySprite sunroom/viewport 5 8 true/pause 1000/showFrame Caroline 22/doAction 6 7/pause 500/doAction 6 7/pause 1000/showFrame Caroline 4/pause 500/warp farmer 5 13/playSound doorClose/move farmer 0 -4 0/faceDirection Caroline 2/pause 100/speak Caroline \"Oh, hi! Good morning, @. I'm glad you came in... / 哦，嗨！早上好啊，@。很高兴你能进来……#$b#I've been meaning to show you this... it's my private sunroom. / 我一直想给你展示一下的……这是我的私人日光室。\"/pause 500/pause 500/speak Caroline \"So, what do you think? / 所以，你觉得怎么样？\"/pause 500/quickQuestion #It's beautiful!#It's very relaxing.#It's too hot in here...#Not as good as my farm!(break)pause 100\\speak Caroline \"Thank you! I've worked very hard to make it this way...$h / 谢谢你！我付出很多努力才布置好的……$h\"(break)pause 100\\speak Caroline \"Yes... when I step in here, I feel calm and relaxed right away. It's really therapeutic!\"(break)pause 100\\speak Caroline \"Oh? I find the warmth soothing, myself.$s#$b#It feels better if you keep still.\"(break)emote Caroline 16\\pause 100\\speak Caroline \"Oh, but you're a professional... For me, it's just a hobby.\"/pause 500/faceDirection Caroline 1/speak Caroline \"You see, this is my sanctuary... a place where I can always find peace... / 你瞧，这里是我的庇护所……是我能一直找到宁静的地方……\"/pause 300/faceDirection Caroline 2/speak Caroline \"And it's a perfect place to drink my home-grown tea! Here, let's have a cup... / 在这里喝我自家种植的茶叶茶也是极好的！来，我们来喝一杯……\"/pause 300/playSound coin/showFrame Caroline 20/pause 1000/playSound sipTea/showFrame Caroline 21/pause 500/showFrame Caroline 20/pause 500/playSound sipTea/showFrame Caroline 21/pause 500/showFrame Caroline 20/pause 500/playSound gulp/pause 1000/quickQuestion Have a cup?#Yes#No(break)farmerEat 614\\pause 1000(break)pause 100\\speak Caroline \"Sure, no problem... / 行，没事……\"/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 0/playSound sipTea/showFrame Caroline 21/pause 500/showFrame Caroline 20/textAboveHead Caroline \"Delicious / 真好喝\"/playMusic SunRoom/pause 1500/speak Caroline \"I love to come in here for a fresh cup of tea every day. / 我很喜欢每天来这里喝一杯新泡的茶。#$b#It's my little ritual...  / 这是我自己的小仪式……#$b#Uh... let me try to explain...$h / 呃……容我解释一下……$h\"/fade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 1000/cutscene greenTea/pause 1000/viewport 5 8 true/pause 1000/speak Caroline \"I hope that makes sense...  / 我希望能说得通……#$b#Life can be pretty hectic, so having a hobby like this is nice. / 有时生活会很忙乱，所以拥有这样的一项爱好也是很不错的。\"/pause 150/showFrame Caroline 0/pause 200/speak Caroline \"Feel free to come here and relax any time you want, okay? / 这里随时都欢迎你过来休息，如何？\"/emote farmer 32/pause 1000/move farmer 0 4 2 true/fade/viewport -5000 1000/pause 1000/end warpOut"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Events/Temp",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "tooBold": "showFrame 6/playMusic none/positionOffset farmer -8 0/positionOffset Elliott 8 0/showFrame Elliott 12/jump Elliott/pause 1000/faceDirection Elliott 1/pause 1000/end dialogue Elliott \"I'm so embarrassed...$8\"",
        "leave": "speak Haley \"Oh, you have to leave already?$s / 你这就要走了？$s#$b#Well... alright. Bye.$s / 唔，那好吧。拜。$s\"/pause 500/move farmer 0 1 1/faceDirection Haley 2 true/move farmer 1 0 2/move farmer 0 1 2/playSound doorClose/warp farmer -1000 -1000/pause 1000/showFrame Haley 22/pause 1000/speak Haley \"Wow... I didn't think ${he^she}$ was that dense.$s / 喔……真没想到${他^她}$那么木讷。$s\"/end dialogue Haley \"I thought you had something important to do...$u\"",
        "decorate": "speak Haley \"Decorate?$s / 装修？$s#$b#Um, okay.$u / 呃，好吧。$u\"/faceDirection Haley 1/speak Haley \"So that's the best thing you can think of doing right now? Here... in this small, dark room with me?$u / 这就是你现在最想做的事情吗？和我……待在这个小黑屋里？$u#$b#Interesting.$u / 有意思。$u\"/faceDirection farmer 0/faceDirection Haley 2/showFrame Haley 22/pause 1000/end dialogue Haley \"Well, the dark room looks great now... Thanks, @.$u\"",
        "honkytonk": "pause 100/speak Sam \"Hi, everyone. We're from Pelican Town... Er... and we're called 'The Alfalfas'$8 / 嗨，大家好。我们是来自鹈鹕镇的……呃……别人叫我们“苜蓿人”。$8\"/speak Sam \"$p 20#This song's about Farming, mining, and chopping wood. / 这首歌写的是做耕种、采矿和砍木头。|$p 8820#This song's about a city in the sea. / 这首歌写的是一座海中城市。|$p 8821#This song's about trains. / 这首歌写的是火车。|Here we go...$8 / 开始！$8\"/playMusic samBand/pause 1200/pause 1666/animate Sebastian false true 104 42 43 52 53/pause 1666/animate Sam false true 208 20 21/animate Vincent false true 208 20 8 21 8/animate Emily false true 208 16 17/animate Leah false true 208 30 31/animate Elliott false true 208 36 37/animate Maru false true 208 29 30/pause 26000/animate Sam false true 208 22 23/pause 12500/animate Abigail false true 104 49 34 35 48/jump Sam/pause 400/animate Sam false true 208 20 21/pause 17500/stopAnimation Sam/stopAnimation Sebastian/stopAnimation Abigail/pause 800/stopAnimation Vincent/stopAnimation Elliott/stopAnimation Leah/stopAnimation Maru/stopAnimation Emily/speak Emily \"$p 78#Wow! Those electronic sounds were far out!$h / 哇哦！这电音很不错啊！$h|Woooh! That was great!$h / 哇！这太棒了。$h\"/speak Leah \"$p 79#Good job! It's a new honky-tonk classic! / 做得不错！这简直是全新的酒吧音乐典范！|Nice work, guys!$h / 你们太厉害了！$h\"/speak Shane \"$p 77#I really loved that heavy breakdown at the end. / 我特别喜欢结尾的处理。|I really enjoyed that bass part. / 我特别喜欢低音的部分。\"/move Sam 1 0 2/speak Sam \"Thanks, everyone!$h / 谢谢大家！$h#$b#But you should really be clapping for @! Without ${his^her}$ help we'd never have decided what kind of music to make in the first place! / 但你们真正应该感谢的是@！没有${他^她}$的帮助，我们根本就不知该去做哪种类型的音乐！\"/faceDirection Sam 2/faceDirection Leah 3/faceDirection Penny 1/faceDirection farmer 3/speak Penny \"So you're like an honorary member of the band, then?$h / 这么说，你就是这个乐队的荣誉成员喽？$h\"/pause 300/faceDirection Penny 0 true/faceDirection Leah 0/faceDirection farmer 0 true/move Sam -1 0 2/speak Sam \"Oh! And don't forget to pick up one of our demo cassettes on the way out... Only 10g! / 噢！走之前别忘了买一盘我们的试听磁带……只要 10 金！\"/pause 1000/mail afterSamShow/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 4000/speak Sam \"That went well! Thanks again for coming with us.$h / 太顺利了！再次感谢你陪我们一起来！$h\"/end dialogue Sam \"Hey. The show was a great success! Thanks again, @.\"",
        "poppy": "pause 100/speak Sam \"Hi, everyone. We're from Pelican Town... Er... and we're called 'The Pelicans'$8 / 嗨，大家好。我们是来自鹈鹕镇的……呃……别人叫我们“鹈鹕人”。$8\"/speak Sam \"$p 20#This song's about Farming, mining, and chopping wood. / 这首歌写的是做耕种、采矿和砍木头。|$p 8820#This song's about a city in the sea. / 这首歌写的是一座海中城市。|$p 8821#This song's about trains. / 这首歌写的是火车。|Here we go...$8 / 开始！$8\"/playMusic samBand/animate Abigail false true 118 49 34 35 48/pause 1890/animate Sam false true 236 20 21/animate Sebastian false true 118 42 43 52 53/animate Vincent false true 236 20 8 21 8/animate Emily false true 236 16 17/animate Leah false true 236 30 31/animate Elliott false true 236 36 37/animate Maru false true 236 29 30/pause 31000/jump Sam/pause 400/animate Sam false true 236 22 23/pause 28500/stopAnimation Sam/stopAnimation Sebastian/stopAnimation Abigail/pause 800/stopAnimation Vincent/stopAnimation Elliott/stopAnimation Leah/stopAnimation Maru/stopAnimation Emily/speak Emily \"$p 78#Wow! Those electronic sounds were far out!$h / 赞叹一声“哇哦”！这电音很不错啊！$h|Woooh! That was great!$h / 哇！这太棒了。$h\"/speak Leah \"$p 79#That was great! It's a new honky-tonk classic! / 这太棒了！这简直是全新的酒吧音乐典范！|Nice work, guys!$h / 你们太厉害了！$h\"/speak Shane \"$p 77#I really loved that heavy breakdown at the end. / 我特别喜欢结尾的处理。|I really enjoyed that bass part. / 我特别喜欢低音的部分。\"/move Sam 1 0 2/speak Sam \"Thanks, everyone!$h / 谢谢大家！$h#$b#But you should really be clapping for @! Without ${his^her}$ help we'd never have decided what kind of music to make in the first place! / 但你们真正应该感谢的是@！没有${他^她}$的帮助，我们根本就不知该去做哪种类型的音乐！\"/faceDirection Sam 2/faceDirection Leah 3/faceDirection Penny 1/faceDirection farmer 3/speak Penny \"So you're like an honorary member of the band, then?$h / 这么说，你就是这个乐队的荣誉成员喽？$h\"/pause 300/faceDirection Penny 0 true/faceDirection Leah 0/faceDirection farmer 0 true/move Sam -1 0 2/speak Sam \"Oh! And don't forget to pick up one of our demo cassettes on the way out... Only 10g! / 噢！走之前别忘了买一盘我们的试听磁带……只要 10 金！\"/pause 1000/mail afterSamShow/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 4000/speak Sam \"That went well! Thanks again for coming with us.$h / 太顺利了！再次感谢你陪我们一起来！$h\"/end dialogue Sam \"Hey. The show was a great success! Thanks again, @.\"",
        "techno": "pause 100/speak Sam \"Hi, everyone. We're from Pelican Town... Er... and we're called 'Xenon Chip 3.0'.$8 / 嗨，大家好。我们是来自鹈鹕镇的……呃……别人叫我们“氙芯片 3.0”。$8\"/speak Sam \"$p 20#This song's about Farming, mining, and chopping wood. / 这首歌写的是做耕种、采矿和砍木头。|$p 8820#This song's about a city in the sea. / 这首歌写的是一座海中城市。|$p 8821#This song's about trains. / 这首歌写的是火车。|Here we go...$8 / 开始！$8\"/playMusic samBand/faceDirection Sam 1 true/pause 1200/animate Sebastian false true 158 42 43 52 53/pause 10100/animate Emily false true 316 16 17/animate Vincent false true 316 20 8 21 8/faceDirection Sam 3 true/animate Abigail false true 158 49 34 35 48/pause 9100/faceDirection Sam 2 true/showFrame Sam 20/pause 1000/animate Sam false true 316 20 21/animate Leah false true 316 30 31/animate Elliott false true 316 36 37/animate Maru false true 316 29 30/pause 20000/jump Sam/pause 400/animate Sam false true 316 22 23/pause 19000/stopAnimation Sam/stopAnimation Sebastian/stopAnimation Abigail/pause 800/stopAnimation Vincent/stopAnimation Elliott/stopAnimation Leah/stopAnimation Maru/stopAnimation Emily/speak Emily \"$p 78#Wow! Those electronic sounds were far out!$h / 哇哦！这电音很不错啊！$h|Woooh! That was great!$h / 哇！这太棒了。$h\"/speak Leah \"$p 79#That was great! It's a new honky-tonk classic! / 这太棒了！这简直是全新的酒吧音乐典范！|Nice work, guys!$h / 你们太厉害了！$h\"/speak Shane \"$p 77#I really loved that heavy breakdown at the end. / 我特别喜欢结尾的处理。|I really enjoyed that bass part. / 我特别喜欢低音的部分。\"/move Sam 1 0 2/speak Sam \"Thanks, everyone!$h / 谢谢大家！$h#$b#But you should really be clapping for @! Without ${his^her}$ help we'd never have decided what kind of music to make in the first place! / 但你们真正应该感谢的是@！没有${他^她}$的帮助，我们根本就不知该去做哪种类型的音乐！\"/faceDirection Sam 2/faceDirection Leah 3/faceDirection Penny 1/faceDirection farmer 3/speak Penny \"So you're like an honorary member of the band, then?$h / 这么说，你就是这个乐队的荣誉成员喽？$h\"/pause 300/faceDirection Penny 0 true/faceDirection Leah 0/faceDirection farmer 0 true/move Sam -1 0 2/speak Sam \"Oh! And don't forget to pick up one of our demo cassettes on the way out... Only 10g! / 噢！走之前别忘了买一盘我们的试听磁带……只要 10 金！\"/pause 1000/mail afterSamShow/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 4000/speak Sam \"That went well! Thanks again for coming with us.$h / 太顺利了！再次感谢你陪我们一起来！$h\"/end dialogue Sam \"Hey. The show was a great success! Thanks again, @.\"",
        "heavy": "pause 100/speak Sam \"Hi, everyone. We're from Pelican Town... Er... and we're called 'Goblin Destroyer'$8 / 嗨，大家好。我们是来自鹈鹕镇的……呃……别人叫我们“哥布林毁灭者”。$8\"/speak Sam \"$p 20#This song's about Farming, mining, and chopping wood. / 这首歌写的是做耕种、采矿和砍木头。|$p 8820#This song's about a city in the sea. / 这首歌写的是一座海中城市。|$p 8821#This song's about trains. / 这首歌写的是火车。|Here we go...$8 / 开始！$8\"/playMusic samBand/animate Abigail false true 125 49 34 35 48/pause 2500/animate Sam false true 250 20 21/animate Sebastian false true 125 42 43 52 53/animate Vincent false true 250 20 8 21 8/animate Emily false true 250 16 17/animate Leah false true 250 30 31/animate Elliott false true 250 36 37/animate Maru false true 250 29 30/pause 31500/jump Sam/pause 500/animate Sam false true 236 22 23/pause 15000/stopAnimation Sam/stopAnimation Sebastian/stopAnimation Abigail/pause 700/animate Abigail false true 250 49 34 35 48/animate Sam false true 500 20 21/animate Sebastian false true 250 42 43 52 53/pause 10000/stopAnimation Sam/stopAnimation Sebastian/stopAnimation Abigail/pause 800/stopAnimation Vincent/stopAnimation Elliott/stopAnimation Leah/stopAnimation Maru/stopAnimation Emily/speak Emily \"$p 78#Wow! Those electronic sounds were far out!$h / 哇哦！这电音很不错啊！$h|Woooh! That was great!$h / 哇！这太棒了。$h\"/speak Leah \"$p 79#That was great! It's a new honky-tonk classic! / 这太棒了！这简直是全新的酒吧音乐典范！|Nice work, guys!$h / 你们太厉害了！$h\"/speak Shane \"$p 77#I really loved that heavy breakdown at the end. / 我特别喜欢结尾的处理。|I really enjoyed that bass part. / 我特别喜欢低音的部分。\"/move Sam 1 0 2/speak Sam \"Thanks, everyone!$h / 谢谢大家！$h#$b#But you should really be clapping for @! Without ${his^her}$ help we'd never have decided what kind of music to make in the first place! / 但你们真正应该感谢的是@！没有${他^她}$的帮助，我们根本就不知该去做哪种类型的音乐！\"/faceDirection Sam 2/faceDirection Leah 3/faceDirection Penny 1/faceDirection farmer 3/speak Penny \"So you're like an honorary member of the band, then?$h / 这么说，你就是这个乐队的荣誉成员喽？$h\"/pause 300/faceDirection Penny 0 true/faceDirection Leah 0/faceDirection farmer 0 true/move Sam -1 0 2/speak Sam \"Oh! And don't forget to pick up one of our demo cassettes on the way out... Only 10g! / 噢！走之前别忘了买一盘我们的试听磁带……只要 10 金！\"/pause 1000/mail afterSamShow/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 4000/speak Sam \"That went well! Thanks again for coming with us.$h / 太顺利了！再次感谢你陪我们一起来！$h\"/end dialogue Sam \"Hey. The show was a great success! Thanks again, @.\""
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Events/Town",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "34/f Penny 500/t 900 1400/w sunny": "50s/49 64/farmer 43 64 1 Penny 59 69 1 George 49 64 0 Gus 37 70 3 Abigail -100 -100 2/skippable/pause 700/emote George 28/pause 500/speak George \"*Sigh*... How am I going to reach that letter in the back?$s / *唉*……我要怎么去拿里面的那个呢？$s\"/move Penny -3 0 0/move Penny 0 -5 3/move Penny -3 0 3/emote Penny 16/pause 300/speed Penny 4/move Penny -3 0 3/faceDirection George 1/pause 400/showFrame Penny 20/pause 400/speak Penny \"Here, let me help you, Mr. Mullner! / 让我来帮你，莫尔纳先生！\"/pause 400/speed Penny 2/move Penny 0 1 3/move Penny -2 0 0/move Penny 0 -1 1/positionOffset Penny 2 0/pause 50/showFrame Penny 5/positionOffset Penny 2 0/pause 50/showFrame Penny 4/positionOffset Penny 2 0/pause 50/showFrame Penny 5/positionOffset Penny 2 0/pause 50/showFrame Penny 4/showFrame Penny 21/move George 1 0 1 true/emote George 16/positionOffset Penny 2 0/pause 50/showFrame Penny 22/positionOffset Penny 2 0/pause 50/faceDirection Penny 1/move Penny 1 0 1/pause 400/faceDirection Penny 0/playSound openBox/pause 600/faceDirection George 3/faceDirection Penny 1/speak Penny \"There you go!$h / 这样就好了。$h\"/pause 300/emote George 12/speak George \"Hmmph. I could've done it myself! And I can certainly move around on my own!$u / 哼。我自己也行！而且我正要自己去拿呢！$u#$b#How feeble do you think I am? / 你看不起我么？\"/move farmer 5 0 1/pause 200/faceDirection George 3/emote George 8/faceDirection Penny 3/speak Penny \"$q 71 null#@? You were watching us? / @？你看到了？#$r 71 50 event_mail1#I was. You did a kind thing there, Penny. / 没错，你做的很好，潘妮。#$r 71 -50 event_mail2 friend_George_25#I was. You should've asked instead of assuming George wanted help. / 你应该不管他的。#$r 71 0 event_mail3#I'm just taking a walk, minding my own business. / 我就散个步，不用管我。\"/pause 400/faceDirection George 2/pause 800/showFrame George 16/pause 500/emote George 28/pause 1000/faceDirection Penny 1/speak George \"*sigh*...No, no... I'm sorry, miss. I shouldn't have gotten so angry.$s / *唉*……不，不……抱歉，女士，我太失态了。$s\"/pause 500/faceDirection George 3/pause 400/speak George \"It was actually very kind of you to help me out. / 非常感谢你的帮助。\"/pause 400/speak Penny \"That's okay, Mr. Mullner. I understand. / 没事，莫尔纳先生。没事我们理解的，\"/warp Abigail 44 1/pause 500/move Abigail 0 8 2 true/move George 7 0 0 false/pause 550/move Abigail -18 0 2 true/warp George -1 -1/playSound doorClose/pause 600/emote Penny 28/pause 700/faceDirection Penny 3/playMusic spring_day_ambient/pause 600/speak Penny \"$q -1 null#It must be difficult to grow old...$u / 看着自己慢慢变老一定是一件很痛苦的事情……$u#$r -1 0 event_old1#I'd rather not think about it. / 我不是很想聊这个话题。#$r -1 0 event_old2#It's just a different part of life. / 这只是生命的另一段旅程。#$r -1 0 event_old3#That's why we should respect our elders. / 所以我们才要尊敬老人嘛。#$r -1 0 event_old4#I'd rather die young... / 我宁可年轻时就死掉……\"/pause 500/emote Penny 40/faceDirection Penny 2/pause 500/faceDirection Penny 3/speak Penny \"Well, it was interesting talking to you, @. I should go.$u / 好吧，和你聊天很有意思，@。我要走了，再见。$u\"/showFrame Penny 20/pause 500/showFrame Penny 12/pause 900/move Penny 6 0 2 true/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/end",
        "itsagift_pennySpouse": "pause 200/pause 500/faceDirection Pam 2/showFrame Pam 25/pause 250/faceDirection Penny 2/speak Pam \"Then... I'll just have to swallow my pride... / 然后……我只需忍辱负重……\"/pause 500/speak Pam \"*ahem*... Thank you, @.$s / *啊哈* ……谢谢，@。$s\"/pause 500/speak Penny \"Mom...$s / 妈妈……$s\"/faceDirection Pam 0/speak Penny \"Don't worry, Mom... we just want to make you happy. No one in Pelican Town looks down on us for being poor.$s / 别担心，妈妈……我们只是想让你开心。鹈鹕镇没有人会因为我们穷而看不起我们。$s\"/faceDirection Robin 1/pause 500/speak Pam \"...I ain't 'poor' anymore, kid... put that thought out of your mind! / ……我不再“穷”了，孩子……别把这个想法留在脑子里！#$b#From now on we'll be like a real family... you hear? / 从现在开始，我们会像一个真正的家庭……听见了吗？#$b#I don't wanna be so bitter all the time anymore...$s / 我再也不想过得如此苦了……$s#$b#I'm gonna try to turn my life around... / 我会努力改变自己的生活……\"/emote Penny 20/pause 100/animate Penny false true 200 0 1 2 3/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 500/positionOffset Penny 0 8/animate Penny false true 100 39/warp Pam -100 -100/playSound coin/pause 3000/fade/viewport -2000 -2000/pause 400/playMusic none/pause 1000/end",
        "3917584/f Shane 3500/O Shane/d Fri/t 800 1700": "distantBanjo/45 71/farmer 48 67 2 Marnie 52 71 0 Jas 51 71 0 Shane -100 -100 2/addConversationTopic shaneSaloon1 0/skippable/move farmer 0 3 2/warp Shane 45 71/playSound doorClose/faceDirection Marnie 3 true/faceDirection Jas 3 true/move Shane 0 1 2/pause 500/speak Shane \"Phew... that was fun.$h / 呼……真好玩。$h#$b#Haven't had a session like that in a while... *urp* / 好久没有像那样来上一盘了……嗝\"/pause 500/emote Marnie 28 true/emote Jas 28 true/emote farmer 28 true/pause 1000/speak Shane \"Welp... I'm all sweaty. Better head back home. / 哎……我全身都是汗。最好快点回家。\"/advancedMove Shane false -10 0 0 -14 -10 0 0 -3 -10 0/move farmer 0 2 3 true/pause 3000/speak Marnie \"Oh no... this doesn't look good.$s / 哦不……这看起来有点糟糕。$s\"/pause 500/faceDirection Jas 1/emote Jas 28/move Marnie 0 1 3 false/faceDirection Jas 2 true/move Marnie -3 0 3/faceDirection Jas 3 true/faceDirection farmer 1/speak Marnie \"@? You'd better keep your eye on him... next time you catch him coming out of the Saloon, you should say something...$s / @？你最好盯着他一点……下次你看到他从餐吧里出来，你得说说他……$s\"/pause 1000/faceDirection farmer 2 true/pause 100/faceDirection farmer 3/pause 1000/end dialogue Shane \"Is everything alright, @? You seem worried...\"",
        "611173/Hn pamHouseUpgrade/o Penny": "50s/71 68/farmer 66 62 2 Robin 67 66 2 Pam 71 71 0 Penny 72 71 0/skippable/move farmer 0 4 2/faceDirection Robin 3/speak Robin \"Hey @! So... what do you think? / 嘿，@！所以……你怎么看？\"/move farmer 0 1 1/faceDirection Robin 2/emote farmer 32/pause 500/speak Robin \"I feel pretty good about it... / 对此，我感觉很好……#$b#In fact, it might be my finest work yet!$h / 事实上，这可能是我最精美的作品了！$h\"/pause 500/faceDirection Robin 1/speak Robin \"Notice the round window... very very difficult to bend the frame like that. / 注意那扇圆窗……非常难以将框弯成那样。#$b#Oh, and the intricate carvings on the door. Took me forever. Did you notice that? / 哦，而且门上还精美的雕刻。花了我很久很久。你注意到了吗？\"/emote farmer 40/speak Robin \"Oh... heh. I guess I'm rambling about wood again... huh?$h / 噢……呃。我想我又在喋喋不休地谈木艺了……嗯？$h\"/move Robin 0 1 3/speak Robin \"Anyway, I'm going to go talk to them... But first I have to ask... / 无论如何，我要去和他们聊聊……但首先我必须要……\"/question fork0 \"Do you want me to tell them you paid for this?#Yes, of course!#No, I'd rather remain anonymous / 你想让我告诉他们是你出的钱吗？#是，当然！#不，我希望保持匿名\"/fork choseToBeKnown/pause 200/speak Robin \"Okay... you stay here, then. / 好的……那么你呆在这里。\"/pause 500/move Robin 0 1 2/move farmer 2 0 2 true/move Robin 0 3 1 false/move Robin 2 0 1/faceDirection Pam 3/move Penny 0 -1 3/move Penny -1 0 3/speak Robin \"Hi there, neighbors... that's a nice new house you got there!$4 / 你好，邻居们……你们这里多了一间漂亮的新房子！$4\"/pause 50/playMusic musicboxsong/speak Pam \"Robin... I... I dunno what to say...$s / 罗宾……我……我不知道该说什么……$s#$b#This is a dream come true... it's all I've ever wanted.$s / 这是一个梦想成真的故事……这是我一直想要的故事。$s\"/faceDirection Pam 2/animate Pam false true 100 25/pause 1000/animate Pam false true 150 26 27/pause 1000/speak Penny \"Robin, thank you so much...$s / 罗宾，非常感谢你……$s\"/speak Robin \"Hey, don't thank me! Someone else came up with the idea... and they paid for everything, too. / 嘿，别谢我！别人想出了这个想法……而且他们付了所有的钱。\"/pause 100/stopAnimation Pam/showFrame Pam 12/faceDirection Penny 2/animate Penny false true 100 23/pause 500/speak Penny \"Then... who?$s / 那么……是谁呢？$s\"/stopAnimation Pam/faceDirection Pam 3/stopAnimation Penny/faceDirection Penny 3/pause 500/faceDirection Robin 2/speak Robin \"I can't say... They insisted on remaining anonymous.$5 / 我不能说……他们坚持要匿名。$5\"/pause 500/faceDirection Penny 2/faceDirection Pam 0/faceDirection Penny 3 true/faceDirection Pam 3 true/faceDirection Robin 1/pause 300/speak Pam \"...They probably stayed anonymous so we wouldn't have to feel obligated to them. / ……他们坚持要匿名，是不想让我们觉得欠他们什么。\"/faceDirection Pam 2/speak Pam \"Whoever you are... You are truly a pure angel...$s / 无论你是谁……你真是一位纯洁的天使……$s\"/pause 300/speak Robin \"Well, I wouldn't go *that* far...$4 / 好吧，我不能说那么*多*……$4\"/jump farmer/animate farmer false true 100 94/pause 500/animate Robin false true 100 32 33/pause 2000/stopAnimation Robin/showFrame Robin 0/stopAnimation farmer/faceDirection Robin 1/faceDirection Pam 0/faceDirection Penny 2/speak Pam \"Penny, from now on we'll be like a real family... you hear? / 潘妮，从现在开始，我们会像一个真正的家庭……听见了吗？#$b#I don't wanna be so bitter all the time anymore...$s / 我再也不想过得如此苦了……$s#$b#I'm gonna try to turn my life around... / 我会努力改变自己的生活……\"/emote Penny 20/pause 100/animate Penny false true 200 0 1 2 3/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 500/positionOffset Penny 0 8/animate Penny false true 100 39/warp Pam -100 -100/playSound coin/pause 3000/fade/viewport -2000 -2000/pause 400/playMusic none/addConversationTopic pamHouseUpgradeAnonymous/pause 1000/end",
        "choseToBeKnown_pennySpouse": "pause 200/addConversationTopic pamHouseUpgrade/speak Robin \"Okay... let's go. / 好吧……让我们一起去。\"/pause 500/move Robin 0 1 2/move farmer 0 3 2 true/move Robin 0 3 1 false/move Robin 2 0 1/move farmer 3 0 1/faceDirection Pam 3/move Penny 0 -1 3/move Penny -1 0 3/speak Robin \"Hi there, neighbors... that's a nice new house you got there!$4 / 你好，邻居们……你们这里多了一间漂亮的新房子！$4\"/pause 250/playMusic musicboxsong/speak Pam \"Robin... I... I dunno what to say...$s / 罗宾……我……我不知道该说什么……$s#$b#This is a dream come true... it's all I've ever wanted.$s / 这是一个梦想成真的故事……这是我一直想要的故事。$s\"/faceDirection Pam 2/animate Pam false true 100 25/pause 1000/animate Pam false true 150 26 27/pause 1000/speak Penny \"@? What are you doing here? / @？你在这里做什么？\"/speak Robin \"What, you didn't tell your wife about this, @?$u / 什么，你没有告诉你的妻子这件事，@？$u\"/faceDirection Robin 0/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 100/faceDirection Robin 1/speak Robin \"@ came up with this idea and paid for the whole thing! / @提出了这个想法，并为整件事买了单！\"/faceDirection farmer 1/stopAnimation Pam/showFrame Pam 12/pause 500/speak Penny \"@... you didn't need to do this... / @……你不需要这样做……#$b#But, thank you. This means a lot to me.$s / 但是，谢谢。这对我来说意义重大。$s\"/stopAnimation Pam/faceDirection Pam 3/stopAnimation Penny/faceDirection Penny 3/pause 300/speak Pam \"This must have cost a fortune, @...$s / 这肯定花了好多钱，@……$s#$b#...To be honest, this is kind of embarrassing. How can I ever repay you for this?$4 / ……说实话，这有点令人尴尬。我该如何报答你呢？$4\"/pause 300/question fork1 \"...#You're my 'Mom'!. No repayment needed!#You can start by treating Penny better... / ……#你是我的“妈妈”！不需要还钱！#你可以从对潘妮好一点开始……\"/fork itsagift_pennySpouse/pause 500/faceDirection Pam 2/showFrame Pam 25/pause 250/faceDirection Penny 2/speak Pam \"...I'm sorry.$s / ……对不起。$s\"/pause 500/speak Pam \"I'll do whatever you say...$s / 我会按你说的做……$s\"/pause 500/animate Robin false true 150 34 35/pause 500/speak Penny \"Mom...$s / 妈妈……$s\"/faceDirection Pam 0/speak Penny \"Don't worry... I understand why you get angry sometimes. Your life hasn't been so easy...$s / 别担心……我明白你为什么有时会生气。你的生活一直不容易……$s\"/stopAnimation Robin/faceDirection Robin 1/speak Pam \"Thanks, kid.$h / 谢谢，孩子。$h#$b#From now on we'll be like a real family... you hear? / 从现在开始，我们会像一个真正的家庭……听见了吗？#$b#I don't wanna be so bitter all the time anymore...$s / 我再也不想过得如此苦了……$s#$b#I'm gonna try to turn my life around... / 我会努力改变自己的生活……\"/emote Penny 20/pause 100/animate Penny false true 200 0 1 2 3/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 500/positionOffset Penny 0 8/animate Penny false true 100 39/warp Pam -100 -100/playSound coin/pause 3000/fade/viewport -2000 -2000/pause 400/playMusic none/pause 1000/end",
        "15389722/j 57": "springtown/62 93/farmer 54 94 1 Lewis 62 94 0 Robin 64 93 3/skippable/move farmer 6 0 1 true/animate Robin false true 100 24 25 26 27 27 27 27 27 27 27 27/pause 200/playSound crafting/pause 1200/playSound crafting/pause 1200/playSound crafting/pause 1200/playSound crafting/pause 500/stopAnimation Robin/faceDirection Lewis 3/speak Lewis \"Ah, hello there, @. You showed up at the perfect time.$h / 啊，你好啊，@。你来得正是时候。$h\"/pause 500/emote farmer 8/move farmer 1 0 0 true/faceDirection Lewis 0/pause 200/speak Lewis \"It's our new 'Special Orders' board. / 这是我们新做的“特别订单”看板。#$b#Robin and I built it from scratch.$h / 是我和罗宾一点一点做出来的。$h\"/pause 500/speak Robin \"Um... Lewis? All you did was hold the nails. / 呃……刘易斯？你只是帮我拿着钉子而已。\"/pause 300/showFrame Lewis 26/playSound slimedead/jump Lewis/shake Lewis 1000/pause 1300/showFrame Lewis 12/faceDirection farmer 1/faceDirection Lewis 3/speak Lewis \"*Ahem*... Ignore her.$5 / 咳咳……别管她。$5\"/pause 400/faceDirection Lewis 0/speak Lewis \"Now, let me explain... / 好，我来解释一下……\"/showFrame Lewis 20/speak Lewis \"You see... with %farm Farm back in business, the local economy has really been picking up. / 是这样的……%farm农场恢复营业，让本地的经济蒸蒸日上。#$b#As a result, some of the local townsfolk have been asking me for a way to source local ingredients for their businesses or personal projects. / 因此，有些镇上的居民想让我给他们做的生意和个人的项目找一个本地的原材料供应商。\"/pause 200/showFrame Lewis 8/faceDirection Lewis 0/speak Lewis \"So, Robin and I came up with the idea of a new 'Special Orders' board, where people can post bigger jobs than would make sense for the old billboard outside Pierre's. / 所以我和罗宾想到了一个主意，就是做一个“特别订单”看板。这样的话，如果委托太大不适合放在皮埃尔的那块布告栏上，就可以贴在这里。\"/faceDirection farmer 0/pause 500/faceDirection Robin 3/move Robin 0 1 3/speak Robin \"Yeah... for example, I plan on requesting some hardwood for a bed I want to make.$h / 嗯……比方说，我打算订一些硬木用来做一个床。$h#$b#I won't put you on the spot, but if you want to help me out you can just accept the job from this board. / 我不会为难你，不过如果你想帮忙的话，直接从板子上接单就行。#$b#Who knows, maybe if the bed turns out well I'll start selling them in my shop!$h / 说不定床能做好的话我会在店里卖……谁知道呢！$h\"/faceDirection farmer 1/quickQuestion #I look forward to helping!#Heh... I dunno... we'll see...(break)faceDirection Lewis 3\\speak Lewis \"I thought so! I wouldn't expect anything less from you, @. / 我就知道！@啊，你从没让我失望过。\"\\emote Robin 20\\speak Robin \"So, can we say that you're... --On Board--?$4\"\\pause 400\\showFrame Lewis 27\\shake Lewis 200\\pause 400\\textAboveHead Lewis \"*groan*\"\\animate Robin false true 150 32 33\\pause 1200\\showFrame Lewis 0\\faceDirection Lewis 3\\speak Lewis \"Well, I'm sure you're busy, so we won't keep you away from your work any longer.#$b#As always, I appreciate your willingness to contribute!$h#$b#Take care, @.\"(break)faceDirection Lewis 3\\emote Lewis 28\\speak Lewis \"Huh... I wouldn't expect such a tepid response from you, @. I'm disappointed.$s\"\\pause 400\\speak Robin \"It's fine, Lewis... there's no pressure to help out.$5#$b#Maybe I can get Sebastian to help. He could use some work away from the computer.\"\\playMusic none\\pause 500\\speak Lewis \"Hmmph... Well, we're done here, Robin.$u#$b#...Wouldn't want to waste any more of @'s precious 'me' time.$u\"\\faceDirection Lewis 1(break)/pause 2000/end",
        "502261/J/w sunny/H": "sweet/-1000 -1000/farmer 53 34 0/broadcastEvent/addTemporaryActor Morris 16 32 -100 -100 2 true/pause 500/speak Morris \"There he is, everyone! Look sharp! / 就是他！快点！^There she is, everyone! Look sharp! / 就是她！快点！\"/specificTemporarySprite jojaCeremony/viewport 53 14 true/viewport move 0 1 8000/pause 9000/move farmer 0 -10 0/pause 4000/speak Morris \"*Ahem*... / *咳咳*……\"/pause 500/speak Morris \"Just a few short years ago, the great innovators at Joja Headquarters came up with a new idea, the Joja Community Development Project. / 就在没几年之前，Joja 可乐总部伟大的发明家们想到了一个绝妙的主意，那就是 Joja 可乐社区计划。#$b#The project was conceived as a way to provide important construction services to the beloved communities we hold so dear...*sniff*... all while generating substantial revenue! / 这个计划能够为我们珍爱的社区提供重要的基础性服务……*哼了一声*…… 同时还能产生大量的财富！#$b#Pelican Town, with its run-down infrastructure, was a perfect testing ground. / 鹈鹕镇正是完美的测试场地。\"/pause 500/speak Morris \"Well, thanks to you, our Community Development Pilot Program has been a major success! / 多亏了你，我们的社区试运行计划获得了巨大的成功！#$b#From repairing old bridges, to fixing buses, to turning piles of rubble into a greenhouse, we've really turned this city around! / 在维修了旧桥，巴士以及温室之后，这个城市已经焕然一新了！#$b#I've also received a big promotion! Hehehe. / 同时我也升职了！嘿嘿嘿。\"/pause 1000/speak Morris \"The president of the company asked me to give you this exclusive gift as a way of saying 'thanks'. / 公司的总裁希望我给你这个礼物以表谢意。\"/playMusic none/pause 1000/awardFestivalPrize joja/null/itemAboveHead joja/null/pause 1000/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/end Position 52 27/end",
        "53/e 55/t 1500 1700": "none/-100 -100/farmer 28 57 1 Evelyn 37 58 3 Gus 30 56 2 Pam 31 56 2 Vincent 27 55 2 Jas 26 55 2 George 37 59 3 Leah 32 61 1 Shane 34 61 3 Robin 27 61 1 Demetrius 28 61 3 Emily 30 58 2 Clint 31 59 3 Harvey 34 57 2 Lewis 35 59 3 Marnie 35 58 3 Elliott 31 63 3 Maru 33 57 2 Sebastian 35 62 1 Abigail 35 63 1 Sam 36 61 2 Penny 37 62 3 Pierre 32 65 1 Caroline 33 65 3 Linus 28 64 1 Haley 28 59 1 Alex 28 58 1/specificTemporarySprite leahShow/skippable/animate LeahEx false true 100 4 5/viewport 33 60 true/move farmer 1 0 1/faceDirection Sebastian 2 true/faceDirection Alex 0 true/move farmer 1 0 1/faceDirection Sebastian 1 true/faceDirection Maru 3 true/move farmer 2 0 1/faceDirection Alex 1 true/faceDirection Maru 2 true/move farmer 0 1 2/faceDirection Shane 0 true/faceDirection Emily 2 true/move farmer 0 1 2/faceDirection Shane 3 true/move farmer 0 1 2/faceDirection Emily 0/move Shane 1 0 2/faceDirection Leah 0/speak Leah \"@! You're here!$h / @！你来啦！$h#$b#Okay... I guess I'd better introduce my pieces. Wish me luck!$l / 嗯……到我介绍的时候了。祝我好运吧！$l\"/pause 300/faceDirection Leah 2/pause 800/faceDirection Leah 1/faceDirection Leah 2/faceDirection Leah 3/faceDirection Leah 2/speak Leah \"Umm... Okay everyone! / 咳咳，大家好！\"/faceDirection Sebastian 3 true/faceDirection Emily 1/faceDirection Demetrius 1 true/faceDirection Elliott 0/faceDirection Pierre 0 true/faceDirection Caroline 0 true/faceDirection Shane 3/faceDirection Sam 3 true/faceDirection Abigail 3/speak Leah \"Thanks for coming to my art show.$l / 多谢光临我的艺术展！$l\"/faceDirection Leah 1/speak Leah \"As some of you know, I came to this town because I wanted to draw inspiration from the beautiful surroundings. / 可能有些人知道，我之所以来这个小镇，是因为我需要从这里美丽的景色中汲取灵感。\"/faceDirection Leah 3/speak Leah \"This place really feels like home now.$h / 现在这里给我的感觉就是家。$h#$b#Okay. I'm going to introduce my sculptures now. / 好吧。是时候介绍我的雕塑了。\"/playMusic jaunty/move Leah -3 0 0/faceDirection farmer 3 true/faceDirection Marnie 3 true/faceDirection Linus 0 true/faceDirection Emily 3 true/faceDirection Demetrius 0/move Leah 0 -1 0/speak Leah \"I haven't named this one, yet. She started out as an exercise in human anatomy, but I ended up seeing her through to completion. / 这座雕塑我还没命名，她起初只是我的练习品。但是我发现了她的美感，并将她做成了成品。#$b#Her expression is intentionally unclear... is she embarrassed, amused, pained? I'll leave that for you to decide. / 她的表情非常暧昧……她究竟是害羞，惊讶还是痛苦呢？这就留给你们自己决定了。\"/pause 1500/move Leah 0 1 2/faceDirection Demetrius 2 true/faceDirection Haley 2 true/faceDirection farmer 2/faceDirection Emily 2 true/faceDirection Clint 2 true/pause 500/speak Leah \"This one's called 'Post-Dimensional Nullspace'. It represents the boundary of human imagination.$u / 这座雕塑的名字是“后维度空白”，它代表了人类想象力的边界。$u#$b#The shape and color came to me vividly when I was in a 'trance state'. / 它的形状和颜色都是在我处于“空想状态”是突然出现的。\"/pause 1500/move Leah 3 0 2/faceDirection Linus 1 true/faceDirection Demetrius 1 true/move Leah 0 1 1/faceDirection Haley 1/speak Leah \"I've been calling this one 'Egg Heads'. I wanted to create an animatronic humanoid statue to toy with the viewer's ability to properly attribute personhood to a physical entity.  / 我一直称呼这座雕塑为“鸡蛋脑袋”。我一直想创造一个能够让观看者感觉到自身人格的人形雕塑。\"/pause 1500/move Leah 0 -1 0/pause 300/faceDirection Leah 2/speak Leah \"And the last one is called 'Wood Sculpture 3'. It's a celebration of my favorite sculpting material... wood. / 最后这座雕塑叫“木雕 3”。这使用我最喜欢的雕塑材料——木头——做出来的作品。\"/faceDirection Leah 3/faceDirection Leah 1/faceDirection Leah 2/speak Leah \"Well, those are my sculptures!$l / 这些就是我的雕塑了！$l#$b#Oh! One last thing. / 噢！还有一件事！\"/faceDirection Leah 0/speak Leah \"I'd like to say thanks to my special friend, @. / 感谢我的朋友，@。#$b#He gave me the idea for this show and the courage to go through with it. I know that sounds cheesy, but it's true. / 是他激发了我举办这次展览的想法，并激励我走到现在。我知道这听上去有些矫情，但这是真的。^She gave me the idea for this show and the courage to go through with it. I know that sounds cheesy, but it's true. / 是她激发了我举办这次展览的想法，并激励我走到现在。我知道这听上去有些矫情，但这是真的。\"/faceDirection Emily 1/faceDirection Shane 3 true/faceDirection Haley 1/faceDirection Elliott 3/pause 400/speak Lewis \"I'm proud of you, Leah! Events like this really breathe life into our little town!$h / 我为你感到自豪，莉亚！这样的展览真的能为我们小镇带来不少生气！$h\"/pause 100/textAboveHead Gus \"Great stuff! / 太棒了！\"/faceDirection Leah 3/speak Demetrius \"I love your art, Leah! 'Post-Dimensional Nullspace' is my favorite.$h / 我很喜欢你的作品，莉亚！我尤其喜欢“后维度空白”。$h\"/textAboveHead Robin \"Great use of wood! / 这真是鬼斧神工！\"/speak Penny \"Thanks for doing this!$h / 真的很棒！$h\"/faceDirection Leah 1/emote Leah 32/faceDirection Leah 2/speak Leah \"Thanks, everyone!$h / 谢谢大家！$h\"/faceDirection Leah 0/emote Leah 20/pause 500/speak Lewis \"Now let's start the bidding on these wonderful art pieces... A marvelous addition to your home!$h / 是时候开始竞拍了……展现你对这些作品的喜爱吧！$h#$b#Do I hear 5000g for the pink one? / 这个粉色的作品，有人出价 5,000 金么？\"/jump Demetrius/mail afterArtShow/viewport move 2 0 8000/pause 5000/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/end dialogue Leah \"Wow! I'm exhausted.#$b#My show was a real success, wasn't it?$h\"",
        "611439/j 4/t 800 1300/w sunny/a 0 54/H": "distantBanjo/53 23/farmer 53 31 0 Lewis 53 23 0 Junimo -3000 -3000 2/broadcastEvent/pause 500/addMailReceived ccDoorUnlock/addQuest 26/skippable/move farmer 0 -3 0/emote Lewis 28 true/move farmer 0 -3 0/pause 300/faceDirection Lewis 2/pause 500/speak Lewis \"Oh, hi there. / 哦，你好。\"/pause 500/move farmer -1 0 0/move farmer 0 -2 0/faceDirection Lewis 0/pause 600/emote Lewis 40/pause 400/viewport move 0 -1 5000/speak Lewis \"What an eyesore...$s / 好丑啊……$s\"/pause 600/faceDirection Lewis 3/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 1/pause 400/speak Lewis \"This is the Pelican Town Community Center... or what's left of it, anyway.$s / 这里就是鹈鹕镇社区中心……或者说社区中心的“遗址”。$s\"/pause 800/faceDirection farmer 0/pause 400/faceDirection Lewis 0/pause 200/speak Lewis \"It used to be the pride and joy of the town... always bustling with activity. / 这里曾经是这个镇子的骄傲……经常举办各类活动。\"/pause 800/faceDirection Lewis 3/pause 500/speak Lewis \"Now... just look at it. It's shameful.$s / 现在……哎。好丢人。$s#$b#These days, the young folk would rather sit in front of the TV than engage with the community. / 现在的年轻人宁可坐在电视前面看一天，也不肯参加社区的活动。\"/pause 800/speak Lewis \"But listen to me, I sound like an old fool.$s / 但是你听我说，虽然说我听上去像个老顽固。$s\"/move Lewis 0 -1 0/speak Lewis \"Joja Corporation has been hounding me to sell them the land so they can turn it into a warehouse...  / JOJA 可乐公司一直在蛊惑我把这个中心卖给他们，他们想把这里改造成一个仓库……#$b#Pelican Town could use the money, but there's something stopping me from selling it... I guess old timers like me get attached to relics of the past... Ah well.$s / 鹈鹕镇真的挺需要这笔钱的，但是我总觉着我不该就这么卖掉它……可能是因为我太恋旧了吧……啊对了，$s#$b#If anyone else buys a Joja Co. Membership I'm just gonna go ahead and sell it. / 如果有人买了 JOJA 可乐的会员的话，我就把这里卖了。\"/pause 1000/speak Lewis \"*sigh*... Here, let's go inside...  / *唉*……进去吧……\"/move Lewis 0 -2 0/pause 300/showFrame Lewis 21/pause 300/showFrame Lewis 20/playSound openBox/pause 500/playSound doorClose/stopAnimation Lewis/warp Lewis -1 -1/move farmer 0 -3 0/playSound doorClose/warp farmer -1 -1/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/changeLocation CommunityCenter/warp Lewis 32 15/warp farmer 32 22/playMusic communityCenter/pause 1000/viewport 32 15 true/viewport move 0 -1 5000/move farmer 0 -10 0 true/move Lewis 0 -4 3 true/pause 5000/faceDirection Lewis 3/pause 500/emote Lewis 8/pause 500/speak Lewis \"Hmm? What's this?... / 嗯？这是什么？……#$b#I guess Vincent and Jas must've been playing in here. / 文森特和贾斯一定来这里玩过。\"/faceDirection Lewis 2/speak Lewis \"This place is even more dilapidated than I remember. / 这里比我记忆中还要破旧。\"/pause 500/temporarySprite 29 8 5 8 50 false 1/warp Junimo 29 8/animate Junimo true true 70 28 29 30 31/playSound coin/pause 400/jump farmer/pause 500/emote Lewis 8/pause 800/speak Lewis \"What? / 什么？\"/pause 500/warp Junimo -1 -1/temporarySprite 29 8 6 8 30 false 1/stopAnimation Junimo/playSound dwop/faceDirection Lewis 0/pause 1000/faceDirection Lewis 1/pause 400/faceDirection Lewis 3/pause 800/faceDirection Lewis 2/pause 600/speak Lewis \"What's the matter? Are you ill?$s / 怎么了？你不舒服么？$s\"/speed farmer 4/move farmer -2 0 0/speed farmer 4/move farmer 0 -1 0/faceDirection Lewis 3/pause 400/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 500/showFrame 96/pause 600/move Lewis 0 1 3/move Lewis -2 0 0/showFrame farmer 0/speak Lewis \"You saw something? Hmm... I wouldn't be surprised if this place was full of rats.$h / 你看到什么了吗？唔……这里有老鼠也是很正常的事情。$h\"/pause 500/temporarySprite 31 14 5 8 50 false 1/warp Junimo 31 14/animate Junimo true true 100 12 13 14 15/playSound coin/pause 400/speed farmer 4/move farmer 1 0 2/jump farmer/startJittering/showFrame 94/pause 1600/playSound dwop/temporarySprite 31 14 6 8 50 false 1/warp Junimo -1 -1/faceDirection Lewis 2/pause 1000/showFrame farmer 0/stopJittering/emote Lewis 40/animate Lewis true false 100 18/pause 900/stopAnimation Lewis/move Lewis 1 0 0/faceDirection Lewis 0/pause 500/speak Lewis \"You're worrying me, @...$s / 你这样我很担心，@……$s\"/pause 700/speak Lewis \"Look, I think I'm going to head home. I need some lunch. / 听着，我要回家了。我需要吃午饭。\"/pause 500/showFrame 96/move Lewis 0 3 2/pause 500/faceDirection Lewis 0/pause 500/showFrame 0/speak Lewis \"Hey. I'll keep this place unlocked from now on... maybe you can help catch that rat if you have some extra time. / 喂。从现在开始，我不会锁这扇门了，你要是有时间的话，可以来抓抓老鼠。\"/pause 600/move Lewis 1 0 2/move Lewis 0 5 2 true/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 500/message \"Strange... / 真奇怪……\"/pause 500/message \"I'll have to come back and explore this building further. / 我会回来继续探索这栋建筑的。\"/pause 800/changeLocation Town/warp farmer 52 20/pause 800/end position 52 20",
        "639373/f Lewis 1500/f Marnie 1500/t 1900 2300/w sunny": "nightTime/68 84/farmer 65 79 1 Lewis 69 83 1 Marnie 69 84 0/skippable/pause 500/faceDirection Lewis 2/pause 200/emote Lewis 28/speak Lewis \"Marnie... we can't. If word got out, it could undermine my position of authority in the town!$s / 玛妮……我们不能这么做，如果事情暴露了，我的地位就完蛋了！$s\"/pause 300/faceDirection Marnie 1/emote Marnie 12/speak Lewis \"You understand... don't you?$s / 你能理解我……的吧？$s\"/pause 1000/speak Marnie \"You care too much about your job, Lewis. There are other things to life, you know.$u / 你太关心你的职位了，刘易斯。生命中还有很多其他美妙的事情。$u\"/faceDirection Marnie 2/pause 500/speak Marnie \"...but yes, I understand. I guess we'll have to keep...us...a secret.$s / ……但是，我理解你，我知道我们必须……保密……$s\"/pause 600/playSound leafrustle/faceDirection Marnie 3 true/faceDirection Lewis 3 true/showFrame Lewis 24/showFrame Marnie 16/jump Lewis/jump Marnie/shake Lewis 2000/shake Marnie 2000/move farmer 4 0 2/showFrame Lewis 12/showFrame Marnie 12/faceDirection Lewis 0/faceDirection Marnie 0/emote Lewis 16/speak Marnie \"Gahh!$4 / 嘎！$4\"/pause 800/speak Lewis \"$q 200 null#@...You overheard everything, didn't you?$s / @……你什么都听到了，是么？$s#$r 200 50 event_secret1#Yes... but I'll keep it a secret. / 是的……但是我会保密的。#$r 201 -100 event_secret2#Yes... and I'm going to tell everyone. / 是的……我要告诉大家。\"/pause 800/move Marnie 0 1 2/pause 800/faceDirection Marnie 3/faceDirection farmer 2/speak Marnie \"Why were you hiding there, anyway?$u / 你躲在这里干什么？$u\"/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 300/jump farmer/pause 1000/speed farmer 4/move farmer -4 0 3/speed farmer 4/move farmer 0 -2 3/speed farmer 4/move farmer -3 0 3/playSound leafrustle/pause 600/faceDirection Lewis 2/faceDirection Marnie 0/pause 300/emote Lewis 8 true/emote Marnie 8 true/pause 1000/end",
        "3917586/e 3917585/O Shane/A shaneSaloon2": "spring_day_ambient/45 71/farmer 47 71 1 Shane 37 72 1 Marnie 48 70 2/addWorldState shanePK/skippable/emote Shane 56 true/move Shane 8 0 0/pause 500/speak Shane \"Okay... I'm ready for another round! / 好……我已经准备好下一局了！\"/pause 500/move Shane 0 -1 0/playSound doorClose/warp Shane -100 -100/pause 1000/faceDirection farmer 2 true/showFrame 0/emote farmer 12 true/emote Marnie 12/speak Marnie \"Alright... we've caught him in the act. Now let's confront him. Take a deep breath... $s / 好了……我们抓他了个先行。现在来处理他把。深呼吸一口气……$s\"/move farmer 0 1 3/move farmer -2 0 0/move farmer 0 -1 0/playSound doorClose/warp farmer -100 -100/move Marnie 0 2 3/move Marnie -3 0 0/move Marnie 0 -1 0/playSound doorClose/warp Marnie -100 -100/fade/viewport -1000 -1000/changeLocation Saloon/warp Shane 33 18/warp Marnie 18 21/warp farmer 19 21/faceDirection Marnie 1 true/faceDirection farmer 1 true/positionOffset farmer 0 16/advancedMove farmer false 6 0 0 -2 8 0 4 10/advancedMove Marnie false 6 0 0 -2 8 0 4 10/specificTemporarySprite shaneSaloonCola/playMusic none/pause 3000/viewport 33 18 true/pause 800/playSound Cowboy_gunshot/pause 200/emote Shane 52 true/playSound Cowboy_gunshot/pause 200/playSound Cowboy_gunshot/pause 200/playSound Cowboy_gunshot/pause 160/playSound cowboy_monsterhit/pause 140/playSound Cowboy_gunshot/pause 170/shake Shane 500/playSound cowboy_monsterhit/pause 200/playSound Cowboy_monsterDie/pause 500/playSound cowboy_gunload/pause 700/playSound Cowboy_gunshot/shake Shane 500/pause 200/playSound Cowboy_gunshot/pause 160/playSound cowboy_monsterhit/pause 140/playSound Cowboy_gunshot/pause 170/playSound cowboy_monsterhit/jump Shane/pause 200/playSound Cowboy_monsterDie/pause 500/playSound cowboy_dead/jump Shane/pause 500/textAboveHead Shane \"Arrgh! / 啊啊！\"/pause 2000/playMusic distantBanjo/textAboveHead Shane \"So close... / 就差一点……\"/pause 3000/faceDirection Shane 1 true/pause 100/faceDirection Shane 2/animate Shane false true 100 18/jump Shane/pause 500/stopAnimation Shane/showFrame Shane 0/emote Shane 16/speak Shane \"Oh, hey! Didn't know I had an audience.$h / 哎呦喂！我怎么有位观众啊。$h\"/faceDirection Marnie 1 true/faceDirection farmer 3/faceDirection Marnie 0 true/faceDirection farmer 0/speak Marnie \"Shane... this is what you've been doing in here?$s / 谢恩……你就一直在这里干这事？$s\"/pause 500/speak Shane \"Yeah! What did you think?$h / 是啊！否则呢？$h\"/faceDirection Shane 1 true/pause 100/faceDirection Shane 0/speak Shane \"I'm completely addicted to this game... / 我完全迷上了这游戏……#$b#I can't help but play round after round... / 我忍不住一盘接一盘地玩下去……\"/pause 500/faceDirection Shane 1 true/pause 100/faceDirection Shane 2/pause 500/animate Shane false true 100 34/pause 500/speak Shane \"I've even reached the number three spot in the global leaderboards... you might say I'm one of the best.$h / 我甚至都排到全球排行榜的前三了……你说我是顶尖玩家之一都不为过。$h\"/pause 500/stopAnimation Shane/pause 100/move Marnie 0 -1 1/speak Marnie \"But... these cans...$s / 但是……这些罐子……$s\"/pause 500/faceDirection Shane 3/pause 200/emote Shane 8/speak Shane \"Oh, that's just Joja Cola... Yeah, yeah, I know... It's bad for the teeth. But it helps me focus... / 哦，那只是 Joja 可乐……是是是，我知道……这对我的牙齿不好。不过这能让我集中精神……\"/pause 1000/faceDirection Shane 2/pause 200/faceDirection Shane 3/faceDirection Shane 2/faceDirection Shane 3/speak Shane \"Wait... did you guys think I was drinking beer?$a / 等等……你们是不是以为我在喝啤酒？$a\"/faceDirection Marnie 2/emote Marnie 28/faceDirection Shane 2/speak Shane \"@? I told you I hadn't been drinking...$a / @？我都跟你说了我没在喝酒……$a\"/question fork0 \"#We were worried...#I'm sorry, I should've believed you / #我们很担心你……#对不起，我应该相信你的\"/fork wewereworried/emote farmer 40/faceDirection Marnie 1/pause 1000/faceDirection Shane 2/emote Shane 40/speak Shane \"...That's alright, @. You're just looking out for me. I get it. / ……没事，@。你们只是在关心我。我懂的。#$b#Look... I know I haven't been perfect... but, I'm trying my best... and I'm gonna keep trying. So you don't have to worry about me. / 你看……我知道我一直不太完美……但是，我在努力做到最好……而且我会一直继续努力……所以你们不必担心我的。#$b#My life is better now than it's ever been. I'm not in such a dark place anymore... / 我的生活已经比以前好太多了。我已经不在阴暗的地方了……\"/pause 500/emote Marnie 20 true/emote farmer 20 true/pause 1300/faceDirection Shane 0/speak Shane \"You know, when I'm playing this game, I become so focused that I can't think about anything else. It really helps when I've got 'the urge'... / 说起来，我玩这个游戏的时候，我会专注到没心思想别的事情。当我有“冲动”的时候这确实很有帮助……\"/faceDirection Shane 2/speak Shane \"Anyway... I'll just... eh... play ONE more round and head home. Okay? / 总之……我就……呃……再玩一局就回家。行吗？\"/pause 1000/emote farmer 32/pause 1000/end dialogue Shane \"You guys must have been really confused when you came in and saw me in front of the arcade machine!$h\"",
        "3917585/e 3917584/O Shane/A shaneSaloon1": "distantBanjo/45 71/farmer 37 67 2 Shane -100 -100 2/addConversationTopic shaneSaloon2 0/skippable/move farmer 0 3 2/warp Shane 45 71/playSound doorClose/move Shane 0 1 2/jump farmer/pause 1000/emote farmer 16/advancedMove Shane false -7 0/pause 500/textAboveHead Shane \"*urp* / 嗝\"/move farmer 0 2 1/speak Shane \"Oh! Hey @. I was just on my way home... / 哦！嘿，@。我正回家呢……\"/pause 500/emote farmer 40/textAboveHead Shane \"Huh? / 啊？\"/pause 2000/speak Shane \"'Were you drinking?'... No!$a / “你刚刚喝酒了？”……没有！$a#$b#Why would you think that?$a / 你怎么会这样想？$a\"/speed Shane 4/advancedMove Shane false 0 1 -5 0 0 -10/pause 500/textAboveHead Shane \"Hmph.. / 哼嗯……\"/faceDirection farmer 2 true/pause 2000/emote farmer 28 true/pause 3000/end dialogue Shane \"...$a\"",
        "6184643/f Haley 3500/O Haley/t 800 1500/w sunny": "sweet/20 90/farmer -100 -100 2 Haley 26 90 3 Penny 16 90 3 Vincent 15 90 1 Jas 15 91 1/addConversationTopic haleyCakewalk1 0/skippable/move Haley -6 0 0/move Haley 0 -1 0/emote Vincent 28/emote Haley 8/faceDirection Haley 3/pause 500/speak Jas \"Ms. Penny? The cover fell off my math book...$s / 潘妮老师？我的数学书的封皮掉下来了……$s\"/speak Penny \"Let me see...$s / 我看看……$s\"/pause 500/move Penny 0 1 3/pause 500/speak Penny \"Oh no... Your books are falling apart...$s / 哦不……你的书都散架了……$s#$b#They're just too old.$s / 它们只是太旧了。$s\"/faceDirection Penny 2/pause 500/showFrame Penny 23/pause 500/speak Penny \"...But new books are expensive, so we'll just have to make do with what we have...$s / ……但是新书都很贵啊，所以我们只能拿现有的凑合用了……$s\"/pause 500/emote Haley 28/jump Vincent/pause 1500/speak Vincent \"Does this mean I don't have to do my homework?$h / 是不是说我就可以不做作业了？$h\"/faceDirection Jas 0/showFrame Penny 27/jump Penny/pause 1000/faceDirection Haley 0/pause 500/warp Haley -1000 -1000/playSound doorClose/pause 1000/end dialogue Haley \"I've been thinking about cake a lot lately...\"",
        "2481135/f Alex 1000/t 900 1600": "sweet/-1000 -1000/farmer 44 65 1 Alex 50 68 1/skippable/specificTemporarySprite joshDog/viewport 53 67 true/pause 3000/speak Alex \"That's a good boy, Dusty. / 真听话，小灰。\"/pause 2000/speak Alex \"You might be the only one around here who understands me.$s / 你大概是唯一一个懂我的人了。$s#$b#No one else has seen the kind of stuff you and I have.$s / 只有你和我有共同点。$s\"/faceDirection Alex 2/pause 700/emote Alex 28/playSound leafrustle/move farmer 6 0 2/pause 500/faceDirection Alex 0/jump Alex/pause 800/speak Alex \"@! Did you overhear me talking?$7 / @！你在偷听我说话么？$7\"/move farmer 0 1 2/question fork1 \"#Yes, I heard everything.#Not really... why? / #没错，我什么都听到了。#没有……怎么了？\"/fork didntHear/pause 500/faceDirection Alex 2/pause 1000/showFrame Alex 27/pause 600/playMusic desolate/emote Alex 28/speak Alex \"I don't really like to talk about it, but I guess I'll explain...$s / 我不太喜欢说这个话题，但是我还是解释一下吧……$s\"/pause 1000/showFrame Alex 0 true/faceDirection Alex 0/pause 500/speak Alex \"Have you ever wondered why I live with my grandparents?$s / 你有没有好奇过，为什么我要和我的祖父母一起住？$s#$b#You see, my father wasn't a good guy... He... Well, he ruined everything for me and my mom.$a / 我的父亲……不是什么好家伙……他……他几乎毁了我和我母亲的人生。$a#$b#Half the time he was gone... The other half he'd drink all night and tell me I'm worthless, that I'd never amount to anything.$a / 从我出生起到现在，有一半的时间他是不在的……而剩下的一半时间，他每天都酗酒度日，然后数落我，痛骂我。$a#$b#I think he resented me for being young... Bitter because he'd wasted his youth doing nothing and had gotten nowhere in life. / 我感觉他是在为自己以前的作为后悔……因为在他年轻的时候一事无成。\"/faceDirection Alex 1/speak Alex \"Well... that's my take on it, anyway. Who knows what was going on in his mind.$a / 唔……我是这么想的，至少。谁知道他脑子里在想些什么。$a\"/pause 800/speak Alex \"One day he left, and soon after that Mom got sick and passed away. I had no choice but to move in with my grandparents.$s / 有一天，他突然离开了，很快我的母亲就生病然后逝世了。我别无他法只能搬到我的祖父母那里去住。$s\"/move farmer 0 1 1/pause 3000/emote Alex 40/faceDirection Alex 0/playMusic spring_day_ambient/speak Alex \"You seem like someone I can trust... That's why I'm telling you this, @. I don't want any sympathy.$s / 你看上去是个很可靠的人……所以我才把这件事告诉你，@。我不需要任何同情。$s#$b#If there's one good thing about my past, it's that it made me strong. / 如果说我的过去有什么使我受益的地方，那就是过去的经历让我变得无比坚强。\"/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 500/speak Alex \"Now... let me show you what Dusty will do for a barbecued steak.$h / 好了……现在我就让你看看小灰吃烤牛排的样子。$h\"/faceDirection Alex 1/faceDirection farmer 1/showFrame Alex 26/specificTemporarySprite joshSteak/playSound dwop/pause 500/pause 500/speak Alex \"Ha! Look at him slobbering. I think he might like steak as much as I do.$h / 哈！看他那口水流的。他和我一样喜欢牛排。$h\"/playSound dogWhining/pause 3000/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/end",
        "502969/w sunny/f Linus 50/j 7/t 2000 2400": "nightTime/-1000 -1000/farmer 72 64 1 Linus 51 58 2 George -100 -100 2 Gus -100 -100 2/skippable/specificTemporarySprite linusLights/pause 800/viewport 55 64 true/pause 1000/move Linus 0 5 1/pause 1000/animate Linus false true 500 20 21/pause 500/playSound trashcanlid/pause 1000/playSound dirtyHit/pause 1000/playSound slimeHit/pause 1000/playSound dirtyHit/pause 1600/warp George 57 64/playSound doorClose/pause 600/stopAnimation Linus/showFrame Linus 22/jump Linus/shake Linus 1000/pause 1000/speed Linus 4/move Linus 0 -1 1/speed Linus 4/move Linus 2 0 3/faceDirection George 3/pause 500/emote George 12/move farmer -14 0 3 true/speak George \"Grr... sounds like those raccoons are back again. Filthy varmints... / 呃……听起来那些浣熊又回来了。这些肮脏的小坏蛋……\"/proceedPosition farmer 58 64/faceDirection George 1/pause 500/speak George \"Ah, you turned up at the right moment, son. / 啊，孩子，你来得真是时候。^Ah, you turned up at the right moment, miss. / 啊，女士，你来的真是时候。#$b#Could you do an old man a favor? Could you go around the corner and scare off those raccoons for me? They've been causin' a real mess. / 你能不能帮帮我这个老头子一个忙吗？你能不能绕过去帮我吓跑那些浣熊？他们把这弄得一团糟。#$b#Thanks. Make sure you give 'em a good scare so they never come back. / 谢谢。你得好好吓吓他们千万别让它们再过来。\"/faceDirection George 0/playSound doorClose/warp George -100 -100/pause 500/move farmer -5 0 3 false/faceDirection Linus 2/faceDirection farmer 0/playMusic echos/pause 1000/showFrame Linus 19/pause 600/emote Linus 28/speak Linus \"It was me... I'm sorry.$s / 是我……我很抱歉。$s\"/pause 500/showFrame Linus 0/pause 800/move Linus -1 0 2/pause 800/showFrame Linus 19/pause 800/speak Linus \"I find a lot of hot, fresh food in these cans... stuff that will go to waste if I don't take it. / 我在这些罐子里发现了很多热乎的、新鲜的食物……如果我不拿走不就浪费了吗。\"/pause 500/move Linus -1 0 2/move Linus 0 2 1/faceDirection farmer 3/speak Linus \"$y 'Do you think there's something wrong with what I'm doing?_Yes, it's disgusting._Disgusting to you, maybe. To me, it's a way of life. And I haven't gotten sick yet. I only eat things that look fresh._No. It's a shame for food to go to waste._Thanks, @. I knew you were an open-minded person. I feel good about what I'm doing. I'm not harming anyone.$h_Yes, it's illegal. That's George's private property._I don't believe in 'private property'. Besides, what do you want me to do? I need this food to survive. Have a heart.$s_No, but you should get a job and stop leeching off others._**Sigh**...#$b#Not everyone's cut out for this world, @. You don't know what it's like to be me. I'm not harming anyone, I just want to live life in my own way. Is that so wrong?' / $y '你觉得我做这些有什么问题吗？_当然，这样太恶心了。_也许，对我来说，这就是我的生活方式。我也没出什么毛病。我只吃看起来新鲜的东西。_没有。浪费食物本身就是可耻的。_谢谢你，@。我知道你是个开明的人。我觉得自己做的挺好的。我没伤害任何人。$h_当然。这是违法的。那是乔治的私有财产。_可我又不信什么“私有财产”。要不，你要我怎么做？我得靠这些食物活下来。有点爱心好吗。$s_虽然没有，但是你应该找一份工作不能当个寄生虫。_**唉**……不是所有人都适应这个世界，@。你不知道我是什么样的人。我不会伤害任何人，我只是想用自己的方式活下去。这错了吗？'\"/playMusic nightTime/pause 800/faceDirection Linus 3/pause 800/faceDirection Linus 1/speak Linus \"You can go on home. I promise I won't rummage in George's can anymore. / 你可以回家了。我发誓我绝对不会再翻乔治的垃圾桶了。#$b#You can tell him you scared off the raccoons for good. / 你可以告诉他你吓走的那些浣熊是有原因的。\"/advancedMove Linus false -3 0 0 6/viewport move -1 1 5000/pause 500/move farmer -9 0 3/warp farmer -100 -100/faceDirection Linus 3/pause 600/animate Linus true true 500 20 21/pause 1000/playSound slimeHit/pause 1000/playSound slimeHit/pause 800/warp Gus 45 71/playSound doorClose/advancedMove Gus false 0 1 3 0 0 -1/stopAnimation Linus/showFrame Linus 22/jump Linus/pause 1000/advancedMove Linus false 0 -2/proceedPosition Gus 48 71/playMusic none/speak Gus \"Wait.$u / 等等。$u\"/faceDirection Gus 0/shake Linus 2000/pause 1000/faceDirection Linus 2/pause 800/showFrame Linus 19/move Gus 0 -2 0 false/speak Gus \"I know what you were doing, Linus.$3 / 莱纳斯，我知道你做了什么。$3\"/pause 500/emote Gus 40/pause 500/speak Gus \"If you need food... just ask. I don't want anyone in Pelican Town to go hungry. / 如果你需要食物……尽管开口。我不想让鹈鹄镇的任何一个人饿肚子。\"/pause 1000/showFrame Linus 0/pause 1000/speak Gus \"Here. I've got a basket of zucchini fritters for you. Just make sure you dip them in my spicy marinara!$h / 给。这是给你的一篮子西葫芦炸团子。一定要蘸着我的辣椒酱吃！!$h#$b#Go on... take it. / 来吧……拿着它。\"/pause 1000/showFrame Linus 19/pause 600/globalFade/viewport -3000 -3000/end",
        "itsagift": "pause 200/pause 500/faceDirection Pam 2/showFrame Pam 25/pause 250/faceDirection Penny 2/speak Pam \"Then... I'll just have to swallow my pride... / 然后……我只需忍辱负重……\"/pause 500/speak Pam \"*ahem*... Thank you, @.$s / *啊哈* ……谢谢，@。$s\"/pause 500/speak Penny \"Mom...$s / 妈妈……$s\"/faceDirection Pam 0/speak Penny \"Don't worry... @ just wants to make us happy. No one in Pelican Town looks down on us for being poor.$s / 别担心……@只是想让我们开心。鹈鹕镇没有人会因为我们穷而看不起我们。$s\"/faceDirection Robin 1/pause 500/speak Pam \"...We aren't 'poor' anymore, kid... put that thought out of your mind! / ……我们不再是“穷人”，孩子……别把这个想法留在脑子里！#$b#From now on we'll be like a real family... you hear? / 从现在开始，我们会像一个真正的家庭……听见了吗？#$b#I don't wanna be so bitter all the time anymore...$s / 我再也不想过得如此苦了……$s#$b#I'm gonna try to turn my life around... / 我会努力改变自己的生活……\"/emote Penny 20/pause 100/animate Penny false true 200 0 1 2 3/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 500/positionOffset Penny 0 8/animate Penny false true 100 39/warp Pam -100 -100/playSound coin/pause 3000/fade/viewport -2000 -2000/pause 400/playMusic none/pause 1000/end",
        "233104/f Sam 2500/t 2000 2400/w sunny/n samMessage": "nightTime/-1000 -1000/farmer 5 90 1 Sam 12 87 2 Vincent 8 22 3 Jodi 6 13 0/viewport 10 86 clamp true/skippable/move farmer 7 0 0/move farmer 0 -2 0/pause 500/speak Sam \"Hi @. / 嗨 ，@。#$b#I wanted to talk to you in private... / 我想和你私下谈谈……\"/faceDirection Sam 1/faceDirection Sam 3/faceDirection Sam 2/shake Sam 1000/speak Sam \"It's kinda cold out here though... let's sneak into my room.$u / 不过外面有点冷……进到我屋里说吧。$u\"/pause 800/move Sam 0 -1 0 true/move farmer 0 -1 0 true/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/changeLocation SamHouse/playSound thudStep/pause 500/playSound woodyStep/pause 200/playSound Ship/pause 500/playSound woodyStep/pause 400/playSound Ship/warp farmer 20 18/warp Sam 20 17/viewport 18 14 true/move Sam 0 -3 2 true/move farmer 0 -3 0 false/pause 1000/faceDirection Sam 3/faceDirection Sam 2/speak Sam \"So... @.$10 / 那么……@。$10#$b#I know I've been talking about nothing but the band for a while now... But I don't want you to think that's all I'm interested in. / 我知道我一直在念叨乐队的事情……但是我不希望你认为我是一个满脑子只有乐队的人。#$b#Um... Er... What I mean is...$8 / 呃……额……我是说……$8#$b#Well, I'm really happy that we've grown so close... Heh.$10 / 我很高兴我们俩的关系能……咳咳。$10\"/move Jodi 0 2 1 true/emote Sam 40/pause 400/speak Sam \"@... do you think of me as... just a friend?$l / @……对你来说……我是朋友还是？$l\"/move Jodi 6 0 0/playSound woodyStep/faceDirection Sam 3/playSound woodyStep/showFrame Sam 33/jump Sam/pause 800/speak Jodi \"Sam? I'm coming in! / 山姆？我进来了！\"/move Sam -1 0 3/speak Sam \"Quick! Hide in the bed!$8 / 快！躲到床下去！$8\"/speed farmer 4/move farmer 0 -2 1/speed farmer 4/move farmer 2 0 1 true/doAction 12 14/faceDirection Sam 3 true/move Jodi 0 -2 1 false/move Jodi 2 0 1/speak Jodi \"What's wrong, Honey? Were you doing something... bad? / 怎么了，亲爱的？你在干什么……坏事么？#$b#I thought I heard some weird sounds coming from your room... / 我好像听到你屋子里传出了奇怪的声音……\"/move Sam 0 -1 3/speak Sam \"No Mom! I was just... doing push-ups! I wanna beat Dad at arm-wrestling some day! ...heh.$8 / 没有，母亲！我只是……在做俯卧撑！我想要和父亲比腕力！……咳咳。$8\"/emote Jodi 16/pause 300/speak Jodi \"Oh! *giggle*... That explains why you're all red and sweaty.$h / 噢！*咯咯*……难怪你满头大汗的。$h#$b#Okay, well good luck. I'll see you in the morning. / 那就祝你好运了。明早见。\"/pause 1000/speak Sam \"Goodnight, Mom.$10 / 晚安，妈妈。$10\"/move Jodi -2 0 2/move Jodi 0 2 0/move Jodi -10 0 2 true/faceDirection Sam 1/emote Sam 28/speak Sam \"Whew... That was close.$h / 呼……好险。$h\"/faceDirection farmer 3/speak Sam \"...@? / ……@ ?\"/pause 800/question fork1 \"#Get out of the bed.#Stay put. / #快出来。#待在原地。\"/fork stayPut/move farmer -2 0 3/pause 600/faceDirection Sam 2/faceDirection Sam 1/speak Sam \"Earlier, I was trying to say... that I really like you, @. I think we could really have something special together... Know what I mean? / 我是想说……我真的很喜欢你，@。我觉得我们俩可以……你知道我是什么意思么？\"/pause 900/speak Sam \"Alright, I said it.$7 / 我终于说出来了。$7\"/resetVariable/emote Sam 40/question fork1 \"#Move closer to Sam.#Head for the window. / #慢慢靠近山姆。#看向窗户。\"/fork rejectSam/playMusic musicboxsong/pause 2000/animate farmer true true 150 6 7 6 8/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 100/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 100/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 100/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 100/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 100/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 100/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 100/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 100/stopAnimation farmer/showFrame Sam 35/pause 1000/showFrame Sam 38 /positionOffset Sam 4 0/animate farmer true true 100 101/pause 3000/speak Sam \"I'm going to be thinking about this night for a long time... / 今晚我会好好考虑一下的……\"/pause 1000/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 6000/end dialogue Sam \"...$l\"",
        "6184644/e 8675611/O Haley/A haleyCakewalk2/t 600 1500/w sunny/i 220": "ragtime/-100 -100/farmer 29 60 2 Haley 27 64 2 Marnie 27 66 1 Caroline 29 66 1 Emily 31 66 2 Jodi 31 68 2 Lewis 25 68 1 Robin 25 70 1 Jas 31 70 3 Vincent 29 70 3 Pam 27 70 0 Clint 27 68 0 Penny 31 64 2 Pierre 25 66 1 Gus 35 66 3 Evelyn 23 67 1 George 24 67 1/removeQuest 127/removeItem 220/specificTemporarySprite haleyCakeWalk/beginSimultaneousCommand/advancedMove Marnie true 2 0 2 0 0 2 0 2 -2 0 -2 0 0 -2 0 -2/advancedMove Caroline true 2 0 0 2 0 2 -2 0 -2 0 0 -2 0 -2 2 0/advancedMove Emily true 0 2 0 2 -2 0 -2 0 0 -2 0 -2 2 0 2 0/advancedMove Jodi true 0 2 -2 0 -2 0 0 -2 0 -2 2 0 2 0 0 2/advancedMove Jas true -2 0 -2 0 0 -2 0 -2 2 0 2 0 0 2 0 2/advancedMove Vincent true -2 0 0 -2 0 -2 2 0 2 0 0 2 0 2 -2 0/advancedMove Pam true 0 -2 0 -2 2 0 2 0 0 2 0 2 -2 0 -2 0/advancedMove Clint true 0 -2 2 0 2 0 0 2 0 2 -2 0 -2 0 0 -2/endSimultaneousCommand/viewport 29 68 true/move farmer 0 4 3/pause 1000/addObject 28 64 220/playSound coin/faceDirection farmer 3/faceDirection Haley 1/speak Haley \"Hey! Oh, good, you brought the cake!... / 嘿！哦，不错，你把蛋糕带过来啦！……\"/showFrame Haley 23/playSound slimeHit/pause 400/showFrame Haley 4/pause 500/showFrame Haley 23/playSound slimeHit/pause 400/showFrame Haley 4/pause 1000/speak Haley \"Seems really moist. Thanks, @. / 看起来水分还很足。谢谢你，@。\"/faceDirection Haley 2/faceDirection farmer 2/speak Haley \"It's a pretty good turnout, huh? / 看人数还挺不错的，是吧？\"/emote farmer 32/speak Marnie \"Um... Haley? When do we stop? M... My legs... *pant* *pant*$s / 嗯……海莉？我们什么时候才能停下来？我……我的腿……(喘)(喘)$s\"/jump Haley/pause 500/speak Haley \"Whoops! Forgot to blow the whistle.$h / 哎呀！忘了吹口哨了。$h\"/showFrame Haley 19/playMusic none/playSound whistle/shake Haley 500/stopAdvancedMoves next/pause 500/showFrame Haley 0/pause 1000/playMusic distantBanjo/pause 2000/speak Haley \"Alright! Everyone should be standing on a numbered square. / 好了！现在每个人都站在一个有编号的方格上。\"/textAboveHead Emily \"I am! / 我站到了！\"/jump Vincent/textAboveHead Marnie \"Yep / 对\"/textAboveHead Pam \"That's right / 是的\"/faceDirection Pam 0 true/faceDirection Marnie 0 true/faceDirection Vincent 0 true/faceDirection Jas 0 true/faceDirection Marnie 0 true/faceDirection Clint 0 true/faceDirection Emily 0 true/faceDirection Caroline 0 true/faceDirection Jodi 0 true/pause 1000/speak Haley \"Your number determines which cake you win! / 你们的编号决定了可以获得哪个蛋糕！#$b#Okay, let's see who gets what... / 好，我们来看看该怎么分配……\"/move Haley 0 -1 1/move Haley 6 0 2/move Haley 0 2 2/speak Haley \"Okay, Let's see here...  / 好，先看这个……#$b#Caroline, what number are you? Okay... you've won... / 卡洛琳，你是几号？好的……你赢得了……#$b#Mayor Lewis' cave carrot loaf... with extra fiber! / 镇长刘易斯的山洞萝卜面包……添加超多纤维！\"/emote Marnie 28 true/textAboveHead Caroline \"Oh, joy / 哦，开心\"/pause 1000/speak Haley \"Emily, you've got... / 艾米丽，你获得……#$b#Pam's chocolate stout cupcakes, with aged bourbon buttercream. / 潘姆的黑啤酒巧克力杯子蛋糕，上面有陈酿波旁威士忌奶油糖霜。\"/emote Emily 32/textAboveHead Gus \"Nice! / 好棒！\"/pause 1000/speak Pam \"You're in for a treat, kid.$h / 你会喜欢的，孩子。$h\"/pause 500/speak Haley \"Next... Jas, you've got... / 接下来……贾斯，你的是……#$b#Clint's wild horseradish cobbler. / 克林特的野山葵酥皮馅饼。\"/emote Jas 28 true/pause 200/speak Clint \"It's an old family recipe. I baked it right in the smelting oven. / 这是我家的一个旧食谱了。我是用冶炼炉把它烤好的。#$b#Oh, um... I may have burnt the bottom a little, so... uh... you might have to peel off a layer of charred matter. But the rest is totally edible. / 哦，呃……底面可能有点烤焦了，所以……呃……你可能得剥掉一层焦掉的东西。不过剩下的部分完全是可以吃的。\"/pause 200/emote Jas 28/pause 500/speak Haley \"Uh, Okay... Next up is Vincent. We've got... / 呃，好的……下一个是文森特。给他的是……#$b# Robin's Triple syrup n' cream strawberry sugar log! / 罗宾的三重糖浆奶油草莓砂糖蛋糕卷！\"/jump Vincent/textAboveHead Jodi \"Oh no... / 哦不……\"/pause 800/jump Vincent/pause 800/jump Vincent/pause 800/speak Haley \"Next up, Jodi. You're gonna take home... / 接下来，乔迪。你可以带回家的是……#$b# Emily's organic red velvet cake... colored with beets! / 艾米丽的有机红丝绒蛋糕……用甜菜上的色！\"/pause 200/textAboveHead Jodi \"Yum! / 好吃的！\"/pause 800/viewport move 0 -1 1500/move Haley 0 -2 3/move Haley -5 0 2/speak Haley \"...and last, but not least: Pam! You're the lucky winner of my husband's deluxe chocolate cake. / ……最后是好东西：潘姆！你很幸运地赢得了我的丈夫的豪华巧克力蛋糕。^...and last, but not least: Pam! You're the lucky winner of my wife's deluxe chocolate cake. / ……最后是好东西：潘姆！你很幸运地赢得了我的妻子的豪华巧克力蛋糕。\"/pause 500/textAboveHead Pam \"Thanks, kid / 谢谢，孩子\"/pause 1000/speak Haley \"Thanks everyone for joining in. We raised over 5,000g! / 感谢大家的参与。我们募集了超过 5,000 金！\"/pause 500/speak George \"What's the money for, anyway? You buyin' a new purse? / 说起来，钱是要用在哪里？你要买新的包？\"/pause 200/faceDirection Haley 1/speak Haley \"Actually... it's for Penny. / 实际上……这是给潘妮的。\"/faceDirection Penny 3/faceDirection farmer 1 true/emote Penny 8/speak Haley \"Penny, the other day I overheard you talking with Jas and Vincent about their school books. It sounded like you could use some help... / 潘妮，那天我无意间听到你跟贾斯和文森特讨论他们的教科书的事情。我想你可以依靠一些帮助……\"/jump Penny/pause 500/textAboveHead Penny \"New books! / 新的书！\"/pause 800/faceDirection Penny 2/speak Penny \"Did you hear that, kids? You're getting brand new school books! / 听到了吗，孩子们？你们可以拿到崭新的教科书了！\"/emote Jas 20 true/emote Vincent 28/pause 500/faceDirection Penny 3/speak Penny \"I don't know what to say... Thank you so much.$h / 我不知道该说什么了……太感谢你们了。$h#$b#...to both of you!$h / ……感谢你们两个！$h\"/emote farmer 32/viewport move -1 0 3000/advancedMove George false 0 -5 24 0/advancedMove Evelyn false 1 0 0 -5 24 0/move Haley 2 0 2/pause 2000/faceDirection Robin 0/faceDirection Pierre 2/speak Robin \"Hey Lewis... since we're funding education without touching the town's coffers, you'll be lowering our business tax, right?$h / 嘿，刘易斯……既然我们资助了教育事业，而且没有碰小镇的金库，你是不是能降低我们的营业税呢？$h\"/pause 500/showFrame Lewis 26/jump Lewis/playSound Duck/positionOffset Lewis -4 0/pause 30/positionOffset Lewis -4 0/pause 30/positionOffset Lewis -4 0/pause 30/positionOffset Lewis -4 0/pause 30/positionOffset Lewis -4 0/pause 30/positionOffset Lewis -4 0/pause 30/positionOffset Lewis -4 0/pause 30/positionOffset Lewis -4 0/pause 30/positionOffset Lewis -4 0/pause 30/positionOffset Lewis -4 0/pause 30/positionOffset Lewis -4 0/pause 30/positionOffset Lewis -4 0/pause 30/positionOffset Lewis -4 0/pause 30/positionOffset Lewis -4 0/pause 30/positionOffset Lewis -4 0/pause 30/positionOffset Lewis -4 0/pause 30/positionOffset Lewis -4 0/advancedMove Robin false 0 -1 3 100/advancedMove Pierre false 0 1 3 100/pause 1500/end dialogue Haley \"It was a big success! Thanks for helping out, honey.\"",
        "831125/f Shane 1750/f Clint 500/f Emily 500/t 1000 1600/w sunny": "spring_day_ambient/-100 -100/farmer 30 87 0 Shane 30 81 1 Clint 34 81 1 Emily 35 81 3/skippable/showFrame Shane 16/move farmer 0 -5 1 true/viewport 34 82 true/pause 800/speak Shane \"Okay guys, do you remember your lines?$u / 好的伙计们，还记得你们的台词吗——$u\"/faceDirection Clint 3/pause 300/speak Emily \"Yes! / 记得！\"/emote Clint 28/faceDirection Clint 1/pause 500/speak Shane \"Ready? Action!$u / 准备好了吗？开始！$u\"/pause 1500/speak Emily \"I thought we had something special... I guess I was wrong.$s / 我本以为我们之间有些什么特殊的情感……看来是我错了。$s\"/pause 500/speak Clint \"I... I... Uh... / 我……我……啊……\"/emote Shane 12/playMusic playful/speak Shane \"Cut! / 卡！\"/speak Clint \"I'm sorry!$s / 对不起！$s\"/faceDirection Clint 3/speak Clint \"It's hard to remember my lines when her face is right in front of me like that...$s / 她这样冲着我说话，我真的很难记起台词诶……$s\"/emote Emily 8 true/emote Shane 8/pause 500/showFrame Shane 17/pause 500/jump Shane/pause 800/speak Shane \"Oh, hey. / 哦，你好。\"/faceDirection farmer 0/speak Shane \"Check out my new camera... / 看看我的新相机。#$b#Joja Co. is having a video advertisement competition. The prize is 10,000g. / JOJA 可乐公司募集广告。奖金是 10,000 金。\"/showFrame Shane 16/pause 500/emote Shane 16/showFrame Shane 17/pause 500/speak Shane \"Hey! I want you to be in this shot... okay? / 嘿！这个镜头你来行么？#$b#Just walk by Clint and Emily in the background while they're talking... It'll give the scene a little more authenticity. / 就在克林特和艾米丽对话的时候从背景里经过……这样这个场景就更真实了。\"/jump farmer/pause 800/move farmer 0 2 1 false/showFrame Shane 16/move farmer 8 0 0/faceDirection Clint 1/speak Shane \"Okay... Ready? / 嗯……准备好了么？#$b#Action!$u / 开始！$u\"/playMusic sadpiano/speak Emily \"I thought we had something special... You said you wouldn't leave me for anything. I guess that was a lie.$s / 我本以为我们之间有些什么特殊的情感……你说过无论发生什么都不会抛下我的。看来是我错了。$s\"/move farmer 0 -8 2 true/pause 500/speak Clint \"No! It's not like that... This is just something I have to do. It's very important to me. / 不！不是这样的……我只是有一件对我来说很重要的事情要做。真的对我非常重要。\"/playMusic none/faceDirection Clint 2/pause 1000/playMusic ragtime/faceDirection Clint 1/speak Clint \"I've just got to try new 'Joja Bluu' cola.$5 / 我想要喝新出的“蓝 JOJA”可乐。$5#$b#It's got three times the sorbitol for a thick, sweet blast. And it's cheaper than water!$5 / 它的甜度是之前的可乐的三倍，而且价格比水还便宜！$5\"/pause 600/speak Emily \"But... But... Isn't soda unhealthy? You promised me...$s / 但……但……碳酸饮料不是不健康吗？你确定……$s\"/pause 600/speak Clint \"Have no fear, my dear. The world-class science team at Joja Headquarters have determined that 'Joja Bluu' does not cause a significant erosion of the stomach lining. So you can drink it whenever you like, as much as you like.$5 / 别担心，亲爱的，JOJA 可乐总部的世界级科学团队已经用实验证明了新出的蓝 JOJA 可乐不会对胃壁造成任何酸性腐蚀。所以喝多少都没事。$5#$b#The real question is... 'When will YOU turn bluu?'... *glug* *glug*... Ahh...$5 / 唯一的问题是……“你会什么时候爱上？”……*咕噜咕噜* *咕噜咕噜*……啊……$5\"/playMusic spring_day_ambient/speak Shane \"Cut! / 卡！\"/faceDirection Clint 3/move Shane 3 0 1 false/speak Shane \"That was perfect. / 完美。\"/move Shane 0 -1 1/faceDirection Clint 2 true/move Shane 5 0 0/speak Shane \"Thanks for the help. $h / 多谢帮助！ $h\"/move farmer 0 2 2/faceDirection Clint 2/pause 1000/speak Emily \"...Clint?$s / ……克林特？$s\"/pause 500/faceDirection Shane 3/faceDirection farmer 3/pause 500/playSound coin/showFrame Clint 39/shake Clint 3000/pause 2000/end dialogue Shane \"What a productive day... I got some great footage.\"",
        "101/f Clint 1500/e 97/k 2123243/k 2123343/o Emily/t 900 1830/a 0 90/!D Emily": "jaunty/11 90/farmer 5 90 1 Clint 6 92 1 Emily 15 90 1 Caroline 16 90 3/move farmer 1 0 2/skippable/emote farmer 16/faceDirection Clint 0 true/emote Clint 16/speak Clint \"@!$4 / @！$4#$b#...You caught me.$s / ……被你发现了。$s\"/pause 500/move farmer 0 1 2/faceDirection Clint 1/emote Clint 28/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 1/pause 200/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 800/speak Clint \"I was planning to ask Emily on a date. I was at her doorstep and everything... but then I heard her coming and I dove into this bush.$s / 我本打算去约艾米丽的，我站在她家门前，那什么……然后我听到她过来，就一头扎进了这个灌木丛。$s#$b#Now I'm waiting until she's done talking with Caroline so I can sneak back into my house.$s / 现在我就等她跟卡洛琳聊完，然后我就能偷偷溜回家了。$s\"/pause 800/emote farmer 12/pause 800/pause 500/faceDirection Clint 0/speak Clint \"What did you just say? You'll never upgrade your tools again if I don't ask her out?$s / 你说什么？如果我不去约她，你就再也不升级工具了？$s\"/faceDirection Clint 1/pause 1500/speak Clint \"You're a villain, @. / @，你真狠。#$b#*sigh* ...alright, I'll do it.$s / 唉……好吧，我去约。$s\"/pause 600/move farmer 1 0 1/move Clint 0 -2 1/speak Clint \"I gotta remember that advice @ gave me in the saloon. / 我得牢记@在酒吧给我的建议。\"/move Clint 8 0 1/stopMusic/pause 500/speak Clint \"Um... Emily? / 呃……艾米丽？\"/pause 800/faceDirection Emily 3/pause 800/faceDirection Emily 1/speak Emily \"Sorry, Caroline. Could you excuse me for a minute? / 抱歉，卡洛琳，能稍等我一会儿吗？\"/pause 500/move Caroline 7 0 0/faceDirection Emily 3/pause 400/speak Emily \"Yes, Clint? / 克林特，怎么了？\"/pause 500/faceDirection Clint 2/pause 400/faceDirection Clint 1/speak Clint \"I was wondering if you'd go w... with... tomorrow, me... *gulp*$4 / 不知道你……明天……跟我……有没有空……（咽口水）$4\"/pause 200/faceDirection Clint 3/pause 300/emote Emily 8/pause 300/faceDirection Clint 1/pause 500/jump Clint/pause 800/speak Clint \"I've got two tickets for the Grampleton Carnival tomorrow. W... Would you go with me? $4 / 我有两张明天格兰普顿嘉年华的票，你……你能跟我一起去吗？$4\"/jump Emily/pause 800/emote Emily 16/pause 400/playMusic musicboxsong/speak Emily \"Sure, Clint! That sounds fun!$h / 好啊！感觉很有意思！$h\"/pause 800/speak Clint \"Really? Okay! I'll pick you up at five.$h / 真的吗？太好了！那我明天下午五点来接你。$h\"/speak Emily \"Okay! See you tomorrow! / 好的！明天见！\"/move Emily 7 0 1/faceDirection Caroline 3/speed Clint 4/move Clint -7 0 2/faceDirection farmer 0/speak Clint \"Did you see that?! I've got a date tomorrow night!$h / 你看到了吗？！我明天晚上有约会了！$h\"/pause 500/jump farmer/pause 1000/faceDirection Clint 1/pause 400/faceDirection Clint 2/speak Clint \"Oh man...I'm so nervous.$s / 妈呀……我好紧张。$s\"/end dialogue Clint \"Thanks for forcing me to do that, earlier. I'm scared, but also very pleased.$h\"",
        "4/f Abigail 1500/t 2100 2400/w sunny": "nightTime/-4442 39/farmer 47 95 0 Abigail 47 87 0 Pierre 52 91 3/skippable/addLantern 735 46 86 1/specificTemporarySprite abbyGraveyard/faceDirection Abigail 2/animate Abigail false true 500 24 27/viewport 47 87 true/pause 4000/move farmer 0 -4 0/pause 500/animate Abigail false false 150 24 25 24 26 0/pause 700/stopAnimation Abigail 0/pause 1500/emote farmer 8/pause 600/animate Abigail false true 100 28 29/pause 1200/stopAnimation Abigail/pause 500/playMusic echos/speak Abigail \"I guess you're wondering why I'm in the graveyard at this hour... / 你是不是在奇怪为什么我这个时间还在墓地……\"/pause 500/move farmer 0 -1 0/pause 400/speak Abigail \"Well, I'm here because it's the best place in town to find some privacy. / 我之所以在这里，是因为这是镇子里仅有的少有人打扰的地方之一。\"/pause 500/emote Abigail 40/pause 250/faceDirection Abigail 1/pause 400/speak Abigail \"And I'm all sweaty because I've been practicing my swordsmanship.$l / 我出了这么多汗是因为我刚刚在练剑。$l\"/emote farmer 16/pause 400/faceDirection Abigail 2/pause 300/speak Abigail \"Hey! What... you think I'm too weak to swing a blade?$a / 嘿！你感觉我太柔弱了？没法挥剑？$a\"/pause 300/faceDirection Abigail 3/pause 500/faceDirection Abigail 2/speak Abigail \"Sorry, I guess I'm getting a little defensive.$8 / 抱歉，我失态了。$8#$b#You see, I want to explore the mountain caves... But I know it's too dangerous to go there unarmed. / 我想要去山里的洞穴里探险……但是如果我空手进去的话太危险了。\"/move farmer 0 -2 0/speak Abigail \"$q 847951 null#You've used a sword before, haven't you? / 你以前用过剑对么？#$r 847951 10 Event_Grave1#Yes, and it's exciting! / 没错，我觉得很刺激！#$r 847951 10 Event_Grave2#Yes, but only in self-defense / 是的，但只是自卫而已#$r 847951 -100 Event_Grave3#Yes, but it's dangerous. You should stay safe. / 没错，但是太危险了。你不应该冒险。#$r 847951 0 Event_Grave4#No / 没有\"/faceDirection Abigail 0/pause 2000/playMusic nightTime/speak Pierre \"Abigail?!$4 / 阿比盖尔？！$4\"/pause 100/faceDirection Abigail 2 true/faceDirection farmer 2 true/emote Abigail 16/speak Abigail \"Dad?$7 / 父亲？$7\"/move Pierre -3 0 0/move Pierre 0 -4 3/faceDirection Abigail 1/faceDirection farmer 1/speak Pierre \"I've been looking all over for you! Your mother wants you to come home and help with dinner!$u / 我找你半天了！你母亲要你回去帮她做晚饭！$u\"/pause 300/faceDirection Pierre 2/pause 700/faceDirection Pierre 1/pause 700/faceDirection Pierre 3/pause 500/speak Pierre \"What are you doing in the graveyard, anyway? This is no place for a young lady!$u / 你在墓地干什么呢？这里可不是年轻女士该来的地方！$u\"/faceDirection Abigail 3/emote Abigail 12/pause 400/faceDirection Abigail 1/speak Abigail \"Mind your own business! You think I should be at home cooking dinner because I'm a girl, don't you?!$a / 管好你自己的事情就好了！因为我是女生，所以我就该回去做饭么？！$a\"/speak Abigail \"You're really stuck in the past, Dad... $a / 父亲，你真是个老古板……$a\"/showFrame Pierre 16/textAboveHead Pierre \"...! / ……！\"/faceDirection Abigail 2/speak Abigail \"Let's get out of here, @.$a / 我们走吧，@。$a\"/showFrame Pierre 0/move Abigail -1 0 2 true/faceDirection farmer 3/move Abigail 0 2 2/faceDirection farmer 2 true/move Abigail 0 3 2 true/faceDirection Pierre 2 true/pause 1000/pause 500/faceDirection Abigail 0/speak Abigail \"Well, are you coming or not?$u / 你来不来？$u\"/pause 600/faceDirection farmer 1/pause 1000/move farmer 0 8 2 true/move Abigail 0 4 1 false/move farmer 8 0 2 true/move Abigail 8 0 2 true/textAboveHead Pierre \"Come back! / 给我回来！\"/globalFade/viewport -4000 0/pause 400/playSound grassyStep/pause 500/playSound grassyStep/pause 300/playSound leafrustle/pause 700/playSound leafrustle/pause 700/message \"Okay, my dad won't find us here... / 好了，这里我父亲就找不到我们了……\"/speak Abigail \"*sigh*... Can you believe my parents were ever young? They don't understand my perspective at all.$8 / *唉*……你能想象我的父母也曾经年轻过么？他们根本不明白我的感受。$8#$b#I know, I know... they grew up in a different era, with different values. It still ticks me off sometimes, okay?$u / 我知道，我知道……他们长大的时代不一样，有不同的价值观……但是有时候我真的无法理解……$u\"/pause 1000/speak Abigail \"Well, thanks for hearing me out @. / 多谢你听我倾诉，@。#$b#Um, now could you help untangle my hair from this bush?$h / 呃，能帮我把卡在树丛里的头发拉出来么？$h\"/pause 500/playSound grassyStep/pause 300/playSound leafrustle/pause 500/playSound grassyStep/pause 200/playSound grassyStep/pause 400/playSound leafrustle/pause 300/playSound leafrustle/pause 600/end",
        "611173/Hn pamHouseUpgrade": "50s/71 68/farmer 66 62 2 Robin 67 66 2 Pam 71 71 0 Penny 72 71 0/skippable/move farmer 0 4 2/faceDirection Robin 3/speak Robin \"Hey @! So... what do you think? / 嘿，@！所以……你怎么看？\"/move farmer 0 1 1/faceDirection Robin 2/emote farmer 32/pause 500/speak Robin \"I feel pretty good about it... / 对此，我感觉很好……#$b#In fact, it might be my finest work yet!$h / 事实上，这可能是我最精美的作品了！$h\"/pause 500/faceDirection Robin 1/speak Robin \"Notice the round window... very very difficult to bend the frame like that. / 注意那扇圆窗……非常难以将框弯成那样。#$b#Oh, and the intricate carvings on the door. Took me forever. Did you notice that? / 哦，而且门上还精美的雕刻。花了我很久很久。你注意到了吗？\"/emote farmer 40/speak Robin \"Oh... heh. I guess I'm rambling about wood again... huh?$h / 噢……呃。我想我又在喋喋不休地谈木艺了……嗯？$h\"/move Robin 0 1 3/speak Robin \"Anyway, I'm going to go talk to them... But first I have to ask... / 无论如何，我要去和他们聊聊……但首先我必须要……\"/question fork0 \"Do you want me to tell them you paid for this?#Yes, of course!#No, I'd rather remain anonymous / 你想让我告诉他们是你出的钱吗？#是，当然！#不，我希望保持匿名\"/fork choseToBeKnown_pennySpouse/pause 200/speak Robin \"Okay... you stay here, then. / 好的……那么你呆在这里。\"/pause 500/move Robin 0 1 2/move farmer 2 0 2 true/move Robin 0 3 1 false/move Robin 2 0 1/faceDirection Pam 3/move Penny 0 -1 3/move Penny -1 0 3/speak Robin \"Hi there, neighbors... that's a nice new house you got there!$4 / 你好，邻居们……你们这里多了一间漂亮的新房子！$4\"/pause 50/playMusic musicboxsong/speak Pam \"Robin... I... I dunno what to say...$s / 罗宾……我……我不知道该说什么……$s#$b#This is a dream come true... it's all I've ever wanted.$s / 这是一个梦想成真的故事……这是我一直想要的故事。$s\"/faceDirection Pam 2/animate Pam false true 100 25/pause 1000/animate Pam false true 150 26 27/pause 1000/speak Penny \"Robin, thank you so much...$s / 罗宾，非常感谢你……$s\"/speak Robin \"Hey, don't thank me! Someone else came up with the idea... and they paid for everything, too. / 嘿，别谢我！别人想出了这个想法……而且他们付了所有的钱。\"/pause 100/stopAnimation Pam/showFrame Pam 12/faceDirection Penny 2/animate Penny false true 100 23/pause 500/speak Penny \"Then... who?$s / 那么……是谁呢？$s\"/stopAnimation Pam/faceDirection Pam 3/stopAnimation Penny/faceDirection Penny 3/pause 500/faceDirection Robin 2/speak Robin \"I can't say... They insisted on remaining anonymous.$5 / 我不能说……他们坚持要匿名。$5\"/pause 500/faceDirection Penny 2/faceDirection Pam 0/faceDirection Penny 3 true/faceDirection Pam 3 true/faceDirection Robin 1/pause 300/speak Pam \"...They probably stayed anonymous so we wouldn't have to feel obligated to them. / ……他们坚持要匿名，是不想让我们觉得欠他们什么。\"/faceDirection Pam 2/speak Pam \"Whoever you are... You are truly a pure angel...$s / 无论你是谁……你真是一位纯洁的天使……$s\"/pause 300/speak Robin \"Well, I wouldn't go *that* far...$4 / 好吧，我不能说那么*多*……$4\"/jump farmer/animate farmer false true 100 94/pause 500/animate Robin false true 100 32 33/pause 2000/stopAnimation Robin/showFrame Robin 0/stopAnimation farmer/faceDirection Robin 1/faceDirection Pam 0/faceDirection Penny 2/speak Pam \"Penny, I'm sorry you had to grow up in squalor... But I'm so happy you've found a good home. We both have, now. / 潘妮，我很抱歉，我让你在垃圾堆中长大……但我很高兴，你得到了一个不错的家。是咱俩现在一起有了。#$b#I'm going to try my best to live a good life, now...$s / 我要尽力过上美好的生活，现在……$s\"/emote Penny 20/pause 100/animate Penny false true 200 0 1 2 3/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 500/positionOffset Penny 0 8/animate Penny false true 100 39/warp Pam -100 -100/playSound coin/pause 3000/fade/viewport -2000 -2000/pause 400/playMusic none/addConversationTopic pamHouseUpgradeAnonymous/pause 1000/end",
        "45/f Sam 1500/t 1200 1600/w sunny": "breezy/-1000 -1000/farmer 20 93 3 Sam 12 90 2 Lewis 28 78 1/skippable/showFrame Sam 25/move Lewis 0 12 3 true/viewport 22 89 true/specificTemporarySprite samSkate1/null/pause 400/faceDirection farmer 1/showFrame Lewis 24/shake Lewis 8000/jump Lewis/showFrame Sam 35/specificTemporarySprite skateboardFly/jump Sam/pause 1000/speak Lewis \"Hey! What do you think you're doing? That's private property!$4 / 嘿！你在干什么！这是私人领域！ $4\"/textAboveHead Lewis \"Sam! / 山姆！\"/pause 500/speak Sam \"Uh... Er... I... I'm sorry, sir.$8 / 啊……额……我……抱歉，先生。$8\"/showFrame Sam 4/emote Lewis 12/showFrame Lewis 12/pause 800/speak Lewis \"*sigh*... The youth these days... Sometimes I wonder if this town isn't doomed.$u / *唉*……现在的年轻人啊……这个镇子要怎么办呀。$u\"/move farmer 0 -2 1/move farmer 6 0 1/faceDirection Sam 2/pause 500/move Lewis 0 1 3/speak Lewis \"You saw what happened, @. What do you have to say about this? / 你刚刚也看到了，@。你有什么想法么？\"/pause 600/question null \"#You're right, sir. Sam should respect private property.#Don't blame Sam. There's nowhere else for him to ride!#I'm staying out of this. / #先生，你是对的。山姆不应该私闯私人领域的。#别怪山姆，他也是实在没地方可以滑了才这样的。#这事我不管。\"/pause 500/splitSpeak Sam \"Fine! I just won't ride my skateboard ever again. Happy?$a~Exactly! If there was a park in town, I could ride there and everyone would be happy.~Hmmph. Alright.$a\"/faceDirection Lewis 2/emote Lewis 12/splitSpeak Lewis \"You're being difficult, Sam. I have no problem with you riding around town, just try not to cause any damage! It's that simple.~Hmmph. I thought you were more mature than this, @.$4~I'll let it slide this time, Sam. But I don't want to see you doing this anymore.\"/faceDirection Lewis 3/splitSpeak Lewis \"Got it?~Sam... I'm sorry I yelled at you. Just please try not to damage anything in the future. Got it?~Got it?\"/faceDirection Sam 1/pause 800/faceDirection Sam 0/emote Sam 28/pause 500/faceDirection Sam 1/speak Sam \"Yes, sir.$7 / 是的，先生。$7\"/pause 600/move Lewis 0 -16 0 true/pause 800/faceDirection Sam 2/pause 800/speak Sam \"...Did you see that trick, though? That was rad.$u / ……你看到我刚刚的特技了么？超帅的。$u\"/faceDirection farmer 0/emote farmer 16/pause 800/end",
        "choseToBeKnown": "pause 200/addConversationTopic pamHouseUpgrade/speak Robin \"Okay... let's go. / 好吧……让我们一起去。\"/pause 500/move Robin 0 1 2/move farmer 0 3 2 true/move Robin 0 3 1 false/move Robin 2 0 1/move farmer 3 0 1/faceDirection Pam 3/move Penny 0 -1 3/move Penny -1 0 3/speak Robin \"Hi there, neighbors... that's a nice new house you got there!$4 / 你好，邻居们……你们这里多了一间漂亮的新房子！$4\"/pause 250/playMusic musicboxsong/speak Pam \"Robin... I... I dunno what to say...$s / 罗宾……我……我不知道该说什么……$s#$b#This is a dream come true... it's all I've ever wanted.$s / 这是一个梦想成真的故事……这是我一直想要的故事。$s\"/faceDirection Pam 2/animate Pam false true 100 25/pause 1000/animate Pam false true 150 26 27/pause 1000/speak Penny \"Robin, thank you so much...$s / 罗宾，非常感谢你……$s\"/speak Robin \"Hey, don't thank me! This was @'s idea... And he paid for the whole thing, too! / 嘿，别谢我！这是@的主意……而且他还为整件事买了单！^Hey don't thank me! This was @'s idea... And she paid for the whole thing, too! / 嘿，不要感谢我！这是@的主意……而且她还为整件事买了单！\"/pause 100/stopAnimation Pam/showFrame Pam 12/pause 500/speak Penny \"@... This is absolutely incredible...$7 / @……简直不可思议……$7#$b#I... I don't know what else to say...$s / 我……我不知道还能说些什么……$s\"/stopAnimation Pam/faceDirection Pam 3/stopAnimation Penny/faceDirection Penny 3/pause 300/speak Pam \"This must have cost a fortune, @...$s / 这肯定花了好多钱，@……$s#$b#...To be honest, this is kind of embarrassing. How can I ever repay you for this?$4 / ……说实话，这有点令人尴尬。我该如何报答你呢？$4\"/pause 300/question fork1 \"...#It's a gift... no repayment needed.#You can start by treating Penny better... / ……#这是一份礼物……不需要报答。#你可以从对潘妮好一点开始……\"/fork itsagift/pause 500/faceDirection Pam 2/showFrame Pam 25/pause 250/faceDirection Penny 2/speak Pam \"...I'm sorry.$s / ……对不起。$s\"/pause 500/speak Pam \"I'll do whatever you say...$s / 我会按你说的做……$s\"/pause 500/animate Robin false true 150 34 35/pause 500/speak Penny \"Mom...$s / 妈妈……$s\"/faceDirection Pam 0/speak Penny \"Don't worry... I understand why you get angry sometimes. Your life hasn't been so easy...$s / 别担心……我明白你为什么有时会生气。你的生活一直不容易……$s\"/stopAnimation Robin/faceDirection Robin 1/speak Pam \"Thanks, kid.$h / 谢谢，孩子。$h#$b#From now on we'll be like a real family... you hear? / 从现在开始，我们会像一个真正的家庭……听见了吗？#$b#I don't wanna be so bitter all the time anymore...$s / 我再也不想过得如此苦了……$s#$b#I'm gonna try to turn my life around... / 我会努力改变自己的生活……\"/emote Penny 20/pause 100/animate Penny false true 200 0 1 2 3/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 50/positionOffset Penny 0 2/pause 500/positionOffset Penny 0 8/animate Penny false true 100 39/warp Pam -100 -100/playSound coin/pause 3000/fade/viewport -2000 -2000/pause 400/playMusic none/pause 1000/end",
        "3917589/n gaveAlexMoney/O Alex/d Mon/d Tue/d Wed/d Thu/d Fri/d Sat": "continue/-1000 -1000/farmer 100 100 2/addWorldState saloonSportsRoom/addMailReceived saloonSportsRoom/message \"It's Sunday... I should swing by the saloon later and see what Alex has been up to! / 星期天了……我应该顺路去一趟餐吧，看看亚历克斯都在干什么！\"/end",
        "didntHear": "pause 400/pause 100/faceDirection Alex 1/speak Alex \"Oh... I was talking to Dusty. / 哦……我在和小灰说话。#$b#He and I have a lot in common, actually.$s / 他和我其实有很多共同点。$s\"/faceDirection Alex 2/pause 1000/showFrame Alex 27/pause 600/playMusic desolate/emote Alex 28/speak Alex \"I don't usually like to talk about it... But we've been friends for a while now and I think I can trust you.$s / 其实我不太想说的……但是我们已经认识有一段时间了，我觉得我可以相信你。$s\"/pause 1000/faceDirection Alex 0/pause 500/speak Alex \"Have you ever wondered why I live with my grandparents?$s / 你有没有好奇过，为什么我要和我的祖父母一起住？$s#$b#My father wasn't a good guy... He... Well he ruined everything for me and my mom.$a / 我的父亲……不是什么好家伙……他……他几乎毁了我和我母亲的人生。$a#$b#Half the time he was gone... The other half he'd drink all night and tell me I'm worthless, that I'd never amount to anything.$a / 从我出生起到现在，有一半的时间他是不在的……而剩下的一半时间，他每天都酗酒度日，然后数落我，痛骂我。$a#$b#I think he resented me for being young... Bitter because he'd wasted his youth doing nothing and had gotten nowhere in life.$a / 我感觉他是在为自己以前的作为后悔……因为在他年轻的时候一事无成。$a\"/faceDirection Alex 1/speak Alex \"Well... that's my take on it, anyway. Who knows what was going on in his mind.$a / 唔……我是这么想的，至少。谁知道他脑子里在想些什么。$a\"/pause 800/speak Alex \"One day he left, and soon after that Mom got sick and passed away. I had no choice but to move in with my grandparents.$s / 有一天，他突然离开了，很快我的母亲就生病然后逝世了。我别无他法只能搬到我的祖父母那里去住。$s\"/move farmer 0 1 1/pause 3000/emote Alex 40/faceDirection Alex 0/playMusic spring_day_ambient/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 500/speak Alex \"You know what? There's no sense dwelling on this stuff... I don't want any sympathy from anyone. / 你猜怎么着？过去的就让它过去把……我不需要任何同情。#$b#You have to look on the positive side of things... My childhood wasn't great, but it did make me strong. I had to be. / 我觉得人还是要乐观一点……我的童年或许不怎么快乐，但至少它让我变得很坚强。我不得不这样。\"/pause 1000/speak Alex \"Here, let me show you what Dusty will do for a barbecued steak.$h / 快看小灰怎么吃烤牛排的。$h\"/faceDirection Alex 1/faceDirection farmer 1/showFrame Alex 26/specificTemporarySprite joshSteak/playSound dwop/pause 500/pause 500/speak Alex \"Ha! Look at him slobbering. I think he might like steak as much as I do.$h / 哈！看他那口水流的。他和我一样喜欢牛排。$h\"/playSound dogWhining/pause 3000/end",
        "463391/f Emily 1000/e 471942/w sunny/z winter/t 600 1700": "EmilyTheme/22 88/farmer -1000 -1000 2 Emily -1000 -1000 2/skippable/pause 4000/playSound doorClose/warp Emily 20 89/move Emily 0 1 2/pause 800/speak Emily \"Ah... Another beautiful day in Pelican Town. / 啊……鹈鹕镇又一个美丽的一天\"/pause 2000/faceDirection Emily 1/specificTemporarySprite parrots1/pause 1000/showFrame Emily 32/jump Emily/pause 1200/showFrame Emily 4/pause 600/playSound parrot/pause 800/playSound parrot/pause 600/faceDirection Emily 2 true/animate Emily false true 250 34 35/pause 3500/stopAnimation Emily/faceDirection Emily 3/pause 1000/textAboveHead Emily \"My friends! / 我的朋友！\"/pause 4000/move Emily 2 0 1/pause 800/emote Emily 8/specificTemporarySprite parrotSplat/showFrame Emily 32/shake Emily 1000/waitForTempSprite 666/specificTemporarySprite parrotSlide/pause 800/speed Emily 4/move Emily 2 0 0/speak Emily \"Oh no! You poor thing!$s / 哦不！真可怜！$s\"/pause 1000/playSound coin/specificTemporarySprite parrotGone/showFrame Emily 30/pause 1000/speak Emily \"Your wing's broken.$s / 你的翅膀断了。$s\"/pause 1000/animate Emily false true 300 28 29 28 30/pause 3000/speak Emily \"Oh, you're a bit different than the others, aren't you? Just like me...$u / 哦，你和其它的有点不同，不是吗？就像我一样……$u\"/pause 2000/speak Emily \"Don't worry. I'll nurse you back to health, little one. Everything will be alright.$u / 不要担心。我会帮你恢复健康，小不点。一切都会好起来的。$u\"/pause 2000/globalFade/viewport -3000 -3000/pause 1000/message \"Emily took the injured parrot into her home and bandaged the wing. / 艾米丽把受伤的鹦鹉带回家并且包扎了他的翅膀。\"/pause 800/message \"He's all set up in her room. But as a token of respect, she didn't give the bird a name. / 它被安顿在她的房间里。但基于对鸟儿的尊重，她并没有给这只鸟儿起名。\"/pause 1000/playSound parrot/pause 1000/end",
        "191393/Hn ccFishTank/Hn ccBulletin/Hn ccPantry/Hn ccVault/Hn ccBoilerRoom/Hn ccCraftsRoom/Hl jojaFishTank/Hl jojaPantry/Hl jojaVault/Hl jojaBoilerRoom/Hl jojaCraftsRoom/Hl JojaMember/w sunny/H": "junimoStarSong/-1000 -1000/farmer -100 -100 0 Evelyn 56 21 0 Lewis 52 33 0 Morris -2000 -2000 0 Jas 62 16 2 Vincent 46 23 1 Emily -2000 -2000 0 Gus -2000 -2000 0 Caroline -2000 -2000 2 Robin -2000 -2000 2 Demetrius -2000 -2000 0 Clint -2000 -2000 0 Pierre -2000 -2000 1 Jodi -2000 -2000 3 Gunther -2000 -2000 0 Willy -2000 -2000 0 Pam -2000 -2000 3 George -2000 -2000 2/broadcastEvent/addConversationTopic cc_Complete/specificTemporarySprite ccCelebration/animate Jas false true 90 16 17 18 19/animate Evelyn true false 500 17 18 17 19 19 19 19/viewport 53 25 true/viewport move 0 -1 8000/move Vincent 1 0 2/move Vincent 0 1 1/move Lewis 0 -9 0 true/move Vincent 8 0 0 false/pause 1000/skippable/jump Vincent/pause 1000/speed Vincent 4/move Vincent 0 15 0/pause 3000/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/warp Lewis 32 22/warp Jas -2000 -2000/warp Evelyn -2000 -2000/warp Vincent -2000 -2000/warp Gunther 24 17/warp Gus 5 5 true/advancedMove Gus true -2 0 4 2000 4 0 4 3000 -2 0 4 2000/warp Pam 8 9/advancedMove Pam true 3 5000 1 0 0 -4 -1 0 4 1000 1 0 0 4 -1 0/warp Emily 16 19/advancedMove Emily true 2 0 2 8000 -2 0 4 3000/warp Pierre 23 10/warp Caroline 24 9/warp Jodi 25 10/warp Willy 40 10/advancedMove Willy true 2 0 4 3000 -3 0 4 3000 1 0 4 3000/warp George 42 18/warp Robin 10 25/advancedMove Robin false 1 0 2 2000 0 -13 16 0 0 -3/warp Clint 46 13/advancedMove Clint false -1 0 4 14000 10 0 0 6 7 0 0 -5/warp Demetrius 47 5/changeLocation CommunityCenter/viewport 7 10 true/viewport move 2 0 21500/pause 6000/move Lewis 0 -12 2/pause 10000/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/warp farmer 32 20/move farmer 0 -9 0 true/viewport 32 10 true/pause 5000/speak Lewis \"I'm not sure how you did it, @... but the community center has never looked better!$h / 我不知道你是怎么做到的，@……但是社区中心从没有变得这么好过！$h#$b#You've done Pelican Town a great service. Everyone in town is pleased.$h / 你为鹈鹕镇立了大功。镇子里的大家都很高兴。$h\"/pause 800/emote Lewis 32/pause 1000/speak Lewis \"As a way of saying 'Thank You', I'd like to present you with this Town's greatest honor... The Stardew Hero Award. You've earned it!$h / 为了表示感谢，我决定授予你本镇最大的荣誉……星露谷英雄奖章。你值得拥有这份荣誉！$h\"/pause 1000/awardFestivalPrize hero/null/itemAboveHead hero/null/pause 1000/faceDirection farmer 0/playMusic none/message \"VOICE: Grumble... Grumble... / 语音：嘟囔……嘟囔……\"/pause 500/textAboveHead Lewis \"Who's that? / 是谁？\"/faceDirection farmer 2 true/move Lewis 1 0 2/move Lewis 0 1 2/pause 500/speak Morris \"Sales have been plummeting! Where have all my customers gone?$u / 销量一直在跌！我的顾客都去哪了？$u\"/playSound doorClose/warp Morris 32 23/textAboveHead Lewis \"Ah, Morris. / 啊，莫里斯。\"/move Morris 0 -9 2/pause 500/faceDirection Morris 1/pause 500/playSound dwop/faceDirection Morris 0 true/pause 50/faceDirection Morris 3/pause 500/showFrame Morris 19/shake Morris 1000/textAboveHead Morris \"Waa..?! / 什……？！\"/pause 500/speak Morris \"All my customers...Here?!?$s / 所有我的顾客……在这？！？$s#$b#This isn't good...$s / 这可不妙……$s\"/move Pierre 0 4 1/textAboveHead Pierre \"How does it feel? / 感觉怎么样？\"/move Pierre 4 0 1/move Pierre 4 0 1/question fork1 \"#Let's be reasonable.#Let's settle this the old-fashioned way. / #我们讲讲道理。#我们用老方法解决这一切吧。\"/fork Punch/showFrame Morris 12/textAboveHead Morris \"Hmmph! / 哼！\"/pause 1000/speak Morris \"It's of no consequence! I'll just run a 75%-off sale and all my customers will come crawling back to me, begging for forgiveness! You'll see!$h / 这都是没有用的。只要我打个二五折，所有顾客都会回头来求我。你会看到的！$h\"/pause 1000/speak Pierre \"No...not this time...$u / 不会的……至少不会是现在……$u\"/faceDirection Pierre 3/textAboveHead Pierre \"Gather 'round, everyone! / 大家，快聚过来！\"/pause 1500/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/stopAdvancedMoves/warp Demetrius 35 14/faceDirection Clint 3/faceDirection Demetrius 3 true/warp Pam 28 15/faceDirection Pam 1 true/warp Gus 28 14/faceDirection Gus 1 true/warp Robin 36 15/faceDirection Robin 3/warp Emily 29 9/faceDirection Emily 2 true/warp Willy 35 16/faceDirection Willy 3 true/warp Jodi 36 9/faceDirection Jodi 2 true/warp Caroline 35 9/faceDirection Caroline 2 true/warp Clint 37 13/faceDirection Clint 3 true/warp Gunther 30 18/warp George 28 16/faceDirection George 1 true/viewport 32 10 true/faceDirection Pierre 2/faceDirection Pierre 3/faceDirection Pierre 0/faceDirection Pierre 3/pause 1000/speak Pierre \"I remember when I first moved to Pelican Town... This building was active and vibrant. / 我还记得我刚搬到鹈鹕镇的时候……这山谷是那么地富有生气。#$b#We worked together to make the town a better place. There was a real sense of community. / 我们共同努力来将小镇建设得更好。那时才真正有一种社区的感觉。\"/pause 1000/playMusic musicboxsong/move Pierre 0 2 3/speak Pierre \"George, you always used to do the crossword puzzle while sipping coffee in the community kitchen. Remember? / 乔治，你总是在厨房里边喝咖啡边玩填字游戏。记得吗？\"/pause 500/faceDirection George 2/pause 500/showFrame George 16/textAboveHead George \"The good ol' days. / 幸福的旧时光啊。\"/move Pierre 0 -2 0/speak Pierre \"Emily, you wove that custom banner for the Stardew Valley Fair. / 艾米丽，是你为星露谷展览会织的标语。#$b#I remember you working on that for years!$h / 我记得你花了几年的时间！$h\"/pause 1000/speak Emily \"It... It was a lot of fun... $s / 很……很快乐呢……$s\"/move Pierre 0 1 1/textAboveHead Pierre \"Willy! / 威利！\"/pause 500/textAboveHead Willy \"Me? / 我？\"/pause 1000/speak Pierre \"Remember when your little crab experiment got out of hand?$h / 还记得你那个玩脱了的螃蟹实验吗？$h\"/pause 500/speak Willy \"Hehe... That I do. We showed up one morning and the place was crawlin' with 'em.$h / 嘿嘿……当然。我们早上到那去时，那全都是小螃蟹。$h\"/faceDirection Pierre 3/speak Pierre \"But Gus saved the day with a brilliant idea... A crab leg feast for the entire valley! / 但是格斯当时想出了个好点子……整个山谷村民的蟹肉盛宴！\"/speak Gus \"I still dream of that garlic butter. / 我还会梦见当时的蒜香奶油呢。\"/pause 100/textAboveHead Robin \"Mmmmm... / 嗯……\"/faceDirection Pierre 0/playMusic none/speak Pierre \"You see, everyone? Our community is what makes Pelican Town special. / 看看吧，大家？只有我们团结一起才能让鹈鹕镇变得与众不同。#$b#When JojaMart came to town we lost sight of that.$s / Joja 超市入驻到镇上时我们还没能意识到这一点。$s#$b#But now, thanks to @, we have a second chance. / 但是现在，多亏了@，我们有了第二种选择。#$b#I'm asking that you join me in boycotting JojaMart! We have the power to reclaim our old way of life! / 我想请你们和我一同抵制 Joja 超市！这样我们就可以夺回我们原来的生活！\"/jump Morris/showFrame Morris 19/pause 1000/textAboveHead Pierre \"Who's with me? / 有谁支持我？\"/pause 3000/showFrame George 0/playMusic springtown/pause 4000/move George 1 0 1/speak George \"I've lived here too long to see this town go to ruin. / 我已经见证了这个小镇一步步被毁掉太久了。#$b#You can count me in!$h / 算我一个！$h\"/pause 500/shake Morris 5000/textAboveHead Demetrius \"I'm in. / 算我一个。\"/pause 250/textAboveHead Jodi \"Boycott! / 联合抵制！\"/shake Morris 5000/faceDirection Morris 0 true/jump Morris/pause 500/textAboveHead Gus \"Me too! / 我也是！\"/pause 500/textAboveHead Gunther \"It's about time! / 是时候了！\"/textAboveHead Robin \"No More Joja! / Joja 滚出去！\"/pause 2000/speak Morris \"I'm done for...$s / 我是不中用了……$s\"/pause 2000/speed Morris 4/shake Morris 5000/move Morris 0 9 2/warp Morris -2000 -2000/playSound doorClose/faceDirection Robin 2 true/faceDirection Demetrius 2 true/pause 20/faceDirection Gunther 2 true/pause 30/faceDirection George 2 true/globalFade/viewport -9999 -9999/pause 4000/message \"Morris and his JojaMart cronies were never heard from again... / 从此再没人听到过莫里斯和他的 Joja 超市朋友的消息。\"/pause 2000/end position 52 20"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Events/Trailer",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "35/f Penny 1000/p Penny": "50s/-1000 -1000/farmer -30 30 0 Penny 12 7 0 Pam -100 -100 0/skippable/specificTemporarySprite pennyMess/viewport 12 7 true/pause 1000/speak Penny \"Ughh... It's so dirty in here.$s / 呃……这里好脏。$s\"/pause 500/warp farmer 12 9/playSound doorClose/pause 500/faceDirection Penny 2/pause 500/emote Penny 16/pause 300/speak Penny \"@! Um... Sorry that it's such a mess. I was about to clean up.$u / @！呃……抱歉，这里很乱，我正准备打扫来着的。$u\"/pause 500/move farmer 0 -1 0/pause 600/emote Penny 32/pause 300/speak Penny \"You'll help me? You really mean it?$h / 你要帮我么？你是说真的吗？$h\"/pause 500/faceDirection Penny 1/faceDirection farmer 1/speak Penny \"Okay, you can get started over there. I'll clean the kitchen. / 你可以从那里开始。我打扫厨房。\"/move farmer 2 0 1/move farmer 0 -2 1/move farmer 1 0 1/move Penny -1 0 0/animate Penny false true 100 24 25/animate farmer false true 100 35/pause 200/playSound dwop/removeSprite 16 6/pause 200/move Penny -1 0 0/animate Penny false true 100 24 25/stopAnimation farmer/faceDirection farmer 0/pause 1200/stopAnimation Penny/removeSprite 10 5/playSound dwop/move Penny -1 0 0/animate Penny false true 100 24 25/pause 900/animate farmer false true 100 41/pause 300/playSound dwop/removeSprite 15 5/stopAnimation farmer/pause 1400/stopAnimation Penny/move Penny 1 0 0/pause 800/warp Pam 12 9/playSound doorClose/stopMusic/move Pam 0 -1 0/faceDirection Penny 2/faceDirection farmer 3/faceDirection Pam 1/pause 500/faceDirection Pam 3/speak Pam \"Whaddya think you're doing?!$u / 你在干什么？！$u\"/faceDirection Pam 1/faceDirection Pam 3/faceDirection Pam 0/speak Pam \"Stop it! I had everything just the way I like it!$u / 停！别乱动我的东西！$u\"/move Penny 2 0 2/pause 500/emote Penny 28/pause 500/speak Penny \"Mom, the house is a total mess. @ and I were just trying to tidy things up a bit. / 母亲，这屋子实在是太脏乱了。@和我想打扫一下。#$b#*sniff* *sniff*... Were you at the saloon just now? You smell like beer...$s / *嗅嗅* *嗅嗅*……你刚刚在酒馆么？怎么身上一股酒味？$s\"/pause 300/move Pam -1 0 3/emote Pam 12/pause 400/speak Pam \"It's none of your damn business where I go!$4 / 我去哪儿跟你无关！$4\"/pause 500/speak Penny \"It IS my business! I don't want you destroying yourself!$a / 这当然与我有关！我不希望你毁了你自己！$a#$b#Don't you realize your choices have an effect on me? Stop being so selfish!$a / 难道说你没有意识到，你的所作所为也会影响我么？能不能不要这么自私！$a\"/faceDirection Pam 0/shake Pam 5000/pause 600/speak Pam \"Selfish? I put a roof over your head and clothes on your back and you call me selfish!? You ungrateful little...$u / 自私？我给你吃给你穿，如今你倒说我自私！？你这个不懂感恩的小……$u\"/pause 500/emote farmer 28/pause 500/faceDirection Pam 1/faceDirection Penny 1/move farmer -2 0 2/move farmer 0 2 3/pause 500/speak Pam \"You'd better go. I'm sorry you had to see this, kid.$4 / 你快走吧。很抱歉让你见到了这一幕。$4\"/pause 500/move farmer -1 0 2/move farmer 0 1 2/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 0/faceDirection Penny 2/pause 700/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 500/warp farmer -40 -40/playSound doorClose/pause 500/move Pam 0 -1 1/pause 300/faceDirection Penny 3/speak Pam \"He's a nice young man... / 他是个好人……^She's a nice young lady... / 她是个好人……\"/speak Pam \"But I don't want you tellin' others to clean up my house! It's embarrassing! You understand?$4 / 我不希望你让别人来打扫我的屋子！这很丢人的好么？你明白么？$4\"/pause 300/faceDirection Penny 2/pause 600/showFrame Penny 23/pause 700/speak Penny \"...Yes, mother.$s / ……我知道了，妈妈。$s\"/pause 1000/mail PennyCleanTrailer/end warpOut",
        "963313/n pamPotatoJuice": "playful/10 7/farmer -100 -100 0 Pam 10 7 0/mail pamNewChannel/skippable/pause 3000/speak Pam \"Heheh... I see the delivery came in.$h / 嘿嘿……我看到东西送到了。$h\"/pause 500/speak Pam \"Let's have a little taste.$h / 来尝尝看吧。$h\"/pause 1000/playSound coin/showFrame Pam 32/pause 2000/animate Pam false true 400 33 34/playSound glug/pause 800/playSound glug/pause 800/playSound glug/pause 800/playSound glug/pause 790/stopAnimation Pam/showFrame Pam 32/pause 400/emote Pam 40/pause 800/showFrame Pam 35/textAboveHead Pam \"Ptooey! / 呸！\"/playSound slimedead/shake Pam 2000/pause 2000/animate Pam false true 400 28 29/speak Pam \"I said potato, not fermented baboon kidney!$u / 我要的是土豆，不是发酵的狒狒的肾！$u\"/pause 2000/end dialogue Pam \"The juice? Yeah, I tried it, kid. $4#$b#How'd it taste? ...Some things are better left unsaid. Let's just leave it at that.$4\"",
        "36/f Penny 1500/p Penny": "musicboxsong/9 7/farmer -30 30 0 Penny 9 7 0/skippable/pause 1000/playSound doorClose/warp farmer 12 9/pause 400/faceDirection Penny 2/pause 300/speak Penny \"@, you came at a good time! / @，你来的正好！#$b#I'm just about finished cooking a new recipe I invented!$h / 我马上就要完成我的新料理了！$h\"/pause 400/move farmer 0 -2 3/faceDirection Penny 1/move farmer -2 0 3/speak Penny \"Let me just finish up real quick. / 再一下下就好。\"/pause 200/faceDirection Penny 0/pause 200/animate Penny false true 120 29 30/playSound crafting/pause 320/playSound crafting/pause 320/playSound crafting/pause 320/playSound crafting/pause 320/stopAnimation Penny/pause 500/playSound openBox/showFrame Penny 29/pause 400/playSound furnace/showFrame Penny 30/pause 1500/playSound clank/faceDirection Penny 0/pause 500/faceDirection Penny 1 true/showFrame Penny 28/speak Penny \"Here, give that a little taste. / 来，给你尝尝。\"/pause 800/faceDirection farmer 2/farmerEat 200/showFrame Penny 4/pause 2500/stopAnimation farmer/pause 500/playSound gulp/animate farmer false true 350 104 105/pause 500/specificTemporarySprite pennyCook/pause 1500/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 500/speak Penny \"$q 72 null#...well? / ……怎么样？#$r 72 50 event_cook1#(Lie) Mmm! That was delicious! / （说谎）嗯嗯！真好吃！#$r 73 -50 event_cook2#Uh... can I get the rest to go? / 呃……我能把剩下的带走吗？#$r 73 0 event_cook3#Well it's definitely unique... how did you get it so rubbery? / 真是特别的味道……你是怎么把它做得那么耐人寻味的？\"/pause 500/speak Penny \"$p 72#Hey, since you're the first person to try it, I'm going to name this one 'Chili de @'.$h / 嘿，既然你是第一个尝这道菜的人，我准备给这道菜起名叫“辣@”。$h|Well, I guess this recipe was a failure...$s / 好吧，我想这次料理失败了……$s\"/stopAnimation farmer/faceDirection farmer 3/pause 600/speak Penny \"Um... so how about we watch a movie or something? / 呃……所以我们要不要一起看个电影什么的？\"/pause 500/move farmer 5 0 0 true/move Penny 5 0 0 true/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/end dialogue Penny \"Thanks for being my taste-tester.$h\""
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Events/Trailer_Big",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "positive": "pause 100/emote farmer 56/pause 500/speak Pam \"Hah! Well, look at me! I'm gettin' real sappy in my old age, aren't I?  ...hehehe.$h / 哈！看我！我那么大的年龄变的多么的笨，是吗？ ……哈哈哈.$h\"/pause 1000/move Pam 0 1 1/move Pam 2 0 0/faceDirection farmer 2/viewport move 1 0 7000/textAboveHead Pam \"Thanks for lendin' an ear, kid / 谢谢你听我唠叨，孩子\"/pause 5000/end",
        "503180/f Pam 2250/A pamHouseUpgrade/A pamHouseUpgradeAnonymous/Hn pamHouseUpgrade": "shaneTheme/-1000 -1000/farmer 18 11 1 Pam 25 9 1/skippable/specificTemporarySprite pamYobaStatue/viewport 25 9 true/move farmer 6 0 1/move farmer 0 -1 1/faceDirection Pam 2/pause 300/speak Pam \"Hey, kid... / 嗨，孩子……\"/faceDirection Pam 1/pause 500/speak Pam \"You caught me prayin'... / 你看到我在祈祷……\"/pause 500/move farmer 3 0 0/move farmer 0 -1 3/pause 500/speak Pam \"This here's my new 'Sign Of The Vessel' statue. / 这个是我的新的“船标”像。#$b#...Ordered it from Joja.com with free 2-day shipping. Don't tell Pierre. / ……在 Joja.com购买可以免2日到货的运费。不要告诉皮埃尔。\"/pause 1000/faceDirection Pam 2/pause 400/faceDirection Pam 3/pause 500/faceDirection Pam 2/pause 500/faceDirection Pam 1/speak Pam \"...I've been settling in to the new house. It's really a great place. Feels like home already. I really do appreciate this new comfort.$h / ……我已经搬到了新的房子。真是个特别好的地方。 已经有家的感觉。我真的特别感谢这个新的慰藉。$h\"/pause 500/faceDirection Pam 2/pause 1000/showFrame Pam 25/pause 1000/animate Pam false true 250 26 27/pause 400/emote farmer 8/pause 500/textAboveHead Pam \"Oh, Sorry... / 哦，对不起\"/pause 1000/stopAnimation Pam/pause 950/speak Pam \"*sniff*... It's just...$s / *嗅*……这只是……$s#$b#...I should be so happy...$s / ……我是应该特别高兴……$s\"/showFrame Pam 0/faceDirection Pam 1/speak Pam \"...But I haven't been able to cut back on the beer... I haven't changed at all...$s / ……但是我还是不能少喝一些啤酒……我一点都没有改变……$s\"/pause 500/emote farmer 28/pause 500/speak Pam \"For a long time, now... I've felt like there's something missing from my life, @... $s / 很长时间以来， 现在……我感觉我的生活总是缺少一些东西，@…… $s#$b#I always thought it was about money... Just bein' poor... ya know? So I figured gettin' this house would solve everything. But ...it didn't.$s / 我总是以为是钱……因为我一直很穷……你知道的？所以我以为我搬到新的房子这一切都会解决。但是……根本没有。$s#$b#So that's... That's why I ordered this statue. / 这就是为什么我买那个雕像的原因。\"/pause 1000/question fork0 \"Say something to Pam:#I'm glad you're feeling hopeful#Sorry Pam, but Yoba isn't real... / 对潘姆说些什么：#我非常高兴你感觉有希望#对不起潘姆， 但是尤巴不是真的……\"/fork positive/friendship Pam -1000/pause 500/speak Pam \"That ain't funny! ...I pour my heart out to you and that's how you respond? What in the void is wrong with you?$u / 那一点都不好笑！……我把我的心都掏出来对你，你就是这样回复我的吗？你是怎么了？$u\"/faceDirection Pam 3/shake Pam 10000/emote Pam 12/pause 1000/speak Pam \"I don't care what you say... I have faith in Yoba! Plenty of us do! Now get out.$4 / 我不在乎你说什么……我对尤巴存有信念！我们可以做很多事情！出去！$4\"/pause 1000/move farmer 0 1 3/move farmer -6 0 3 true/end"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Events/WizardHouse",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "418172/n hasPickedUpMagicInk": "WizardSong/2 14/farmer 3 14 3 Wizard 1 14 1/skippable/pause 1000/speak Wizard \"You've found my ink! Excellent. / 你找到了墨水！太好了\"/move Wizard 1 0 1/pause 1000/speak Wizard \"Er... / 呃……\"/faceDirection Wizard 2/pause 500/showFrame Wizard 18/pause 500/speak Wizard \"Did you... happen to see my ex-wife? / 你有……看到我的前妻吗？#$b#No? Well, what about her house...? / 没有？好吧，那她的家呢……？#$b#Do you think she lives alone? Or...$h / 你觉得她是一个人住吗？还是……$h\"/pause 500/showFrame Wizard 0/emote Wizard 12/pause 500/faceDirection Wizard 3/pause 500/speak Wizard \"...Actually, don't tell me... I don't want to know. / ……哎，还是别告诉我了……我不想知道。\"/pause 500/pause 500/faceDirection Wizard 2/pause 500/speak Wizard \"Anyway... you must be wondering about your reward. Here... / ……好吧……你一定很好奇你的奖赏。在这……\"/move Wizard -1 0 1/pause 800/faceDirection Wizard 2/pause 1000/showFrame Wizard 16/pause 800/specificTemporarySprite arcaneBook/playSound fireball/shake Wizard 500/pause 4000/faceDirection farmer 0/faceDirection Wizard 1/faceDirection Wizard 0/pause 500/speak Wizard \"It's a book of summoning. / 这是本召唤之书。#$b#The arcane potential is immense... but I'll make it simple for you. / 神秘的潜力是无限的……我来帮你简单化一下吧。#$b#By using this book, you can summon magic buildings directly to your farm. / 使用这本书后，你能直接召唤魔法建筑物到你的农场里。#$b#I think you'll find it useful. / 我想你会觉得这个有用的。\"/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 3/faceDirection Wizard 1/speak Wizard \"Oh, I almost forgot to say... ahem... Thank you. / 哦，我差点忘了说了……啊哼……谢谢你。\"/pause 1000/emote farmer 32/pause 800/end",
        "112/n seenJunimoNote": "WizardSong/-1000 -1000/farmer 8 24 0 Wizard 10 15 2 Junimo -2000 -2000 2/skippable/addConversationTopic cc_Begin/showFrame Wizard 20/viewport 8 18 true/move farmer 0 -3 0/pause 2000/speak Wizard \"Ah... Come in. / 哎呀……进来。\"/pause 800/animate Wizard false false 100 20 21 22 0/playSound dwop/pause 1000/stopAnimation Wizard/move Wizard -2 0 3 false/move Wizard 0 2 2/pause 1500/speak Wizard \"I am Rasmodius... Seeker of the arcane truths. / 我是拉斯莫迪斯……奥术的追寻者。#$b#Mediary between physical and ethereal. / 联系现实和超自然的媒介。#$b#Master of the seven elementals. / 七种元素的主人。#$b#Keeper of the sacred cha-... you get the point. / 守护圣——……你应该已经明白了。\"/pause 1000/move Wizard 0 1 2/speak Wizard \"And you... @. The one whose arrival I have long foreseen. / 而你@我早就预见了你的到来。\"/pause 1500/speak Wizard \"Here, I'd like to show you something. / 来，我要给你看样东西。\"/pause 500/faceDirection Wizard 1/playMusic none/pause 800/speak Wizard \"Behold! / 看哪！\"/playMusic clubloop/pause 1000/showFrame Wizard 19/playSound wand/screenFlash .8/warp Junimo 10 17/specificTemporarySprite junimoCage/pause 3000/shake Junimo 800/playSound junimoMeep1/pause 1000/shake Junimo 800/playSound junimoMeep1/pause 1000/faceDirection Wizard 1 true/showFrame Wizard 4/pause 2000/shake Junimo 800/playSound junimoMeep1/pause 1000/speak Wizard \"You've seen one before, haven't you? / 你曾经见过一次，对吧？\"/move Wizard 0 -1 1/pause 1000/shake Junimo 800/playSound junimoMeep1/pause 1000/speak Wizard \"They call themselves the 'Junimos'... / 他们自称“祝尼魔”……#$b#Mysterious spirits, these ones... For some reason, they refuse to speak with me. / 这些，神秘的精灵……出于某种原因，拒绝和我说话。\"/pause 1000/playSound dwop/faceDirection Wizard 2 true/showFrame Wizard 16/pause 500/playSound wand/screenFlash .8/warp Junimo -3000 -3000/specificTemporarySprite junimoCageGone/playMusic WizardSong/pause 1000/showFrame Wizard 0/pause 500/speak Wizard \"I'm not sure why they've moved into the community center, but you have no reason to fear them. / 我不清楚为什么他们要搬进社区活动中心，但是你没理由害怕他们。\"/pause 1000/move farmer 0 -1 0/emote farmer 48/pause 1000/speak Wizard \"Hmmm? You found a golden scroll written in an unknown language? / 嗯？你找到了一个写着未知语言的金色卷轴？#$b#Most interesting... / 真有意思……\"/move Wizard 0 1 2/speak Wizard \"Stay here. I'm going to see for myself. I'll return shortly. / 你留在这儿。我要亲自去看一看。我马上就会回来的。\"/pause 1000/playSound shwip/faceDirection Wizard 3 true/pause 50/faceDirection Wizard 0 true/pause 50/faceDirection Wizard 1 true/pause 50/faceDirection Wizard 2 true/pause 50/showFrame Wizard 16/pause 500/playSound wand/warp Wizard -3000 -3000/specificTemporarySprite wizardWarp/pause 2000/faceDirection farmer 1/faceDirection farmer 3/faceDirection farmer 0/pause 2000/playSound dwop/faceDirection Wizard 0 true/faceDirection farmer 1 true/pause 50/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 1500/playSound doorClose/warp Wizard 8 24/faceDirection farmer 2 true/showFrame farmer 94/startJittering/move Wizard 0 -1 0/stopJittering/showFrame farmer 0/move Wizard 0 -2 0/speak Wizard \"I found the note... / 我找到了笔记……\"/move Wizard -2 0 3/pause 800/speak Wizard \"The language is obscure, but I was able to decipher it: / 这种语言很难懂，但是我能破解它：\"/pause 1000/message \"We, the Junimo, are happy to aid you. In return, we ask for gifts of the valley. If you are one with the forest then you will see the true nature of this scroll. / 我们，祝尼魔，很高兴能帮助你。作为回报，我们想要谷中的礼物。如果你是能和森林融为一体的人，那你就能看到卷轴真实的样子。\"/pause 500/move Wizard 0 -2 3/faceDirection farmer 3 true/move Wizard -3 0 2/pause 1000/showFrame Wizard 18/emote Wizard 40/speak Wizard \"Hmm... 'One with the forest'... What do they mean? / 唔……“和森林融为一体的人”……这是什么意思？\"/pause 1000/speak Wizard \"...*sniff*...*sniff*... / ……*嗅嗅*……*嗅嗅*……\"/pause 1500/showFrame Wizard 0/jump Wizard/pause 800/speak Wizard \"Ah-hah!$h / 啊哈！$h\"/pause 800/faceDirection Wizard 1/speak Wizard \"Come here!$h / 过来！$h\"/pause 500/move farmer -2 0 0/move farmer 0 -1 3/move farmer -2 0 3/move Wizard -1 0 2/move farmer -1 0 2/pause 500/speak Wizard \"My cauldron is bubbling with ingredients from the forest.$h / 我的大锅里滚着各种森林里的素材。$h#$b#Baby fern, moss grub, caramel-top toadstool... Can you smell it?$h / 蕨草，苔藓幼虫，焦糖顶毒蘑菇……你闻到了吗？$h\"/pause 500/showFrame Wizard 18/showFrame 96/pause 1000/speak Wizard \"Here. Drink up. Let the essence of the forest permeate your body.$h / 给。喝下去。让森林的精髓渗入你的身体。$h\"/pause 800/emote farmer 28/showFrame Wizard 19/pause 800/showFrame farmer 90/pause 1000/farmerEat 184/pause 4000/playSound gulp/animate farmer false true 350 104 105/pause 4000/specificTemporarySprite farmerForestVision/pause 7000/pause 19500/globalFade .008/specificTemporarySprite junimoCageGone2/viewport -1000 -1000/playMusic none/pause 2000/playSound reward/pause 300/message \"You've gained the power of forest magic! Now you can decipher the true meaning of the Junimo scrolls. / 你得到了森林的魔力！现在你能读懂祝尼魔卷轴的真正含义了。\"/end warpOut"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Events/Woods",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "2123343/e 2111294/t 2200 2540/w sunny/F/D Emily": "nightTime/-1000 -1000/farmer 29 14 3 Emily 26 14 1/skippable/specificTemporarySprite EmilyCamping/viewport 27 12 true/pause 5000/faceDirection Emily 2/pause 1000/faceDirection Emily 3/pause 1500/faceDirection Emily 2 true/pause 50/faceDirection Emily 1/pause 1000/speak Emily \"Well, this is fun, isn't it? / 好吧，这很有趣，不是吗？\"/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 500/faceDirection Emily 2/pause 1000/speak Emily \"Kind of spooky, actually...$u / 有点令人毛骨悚然，其实……$u\"/pause 1000/playSound grunt/pause 800/faceDirection Emily 0/emote Emily 8/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 0/move Emily 0 -1 1/move Emily 1 0 2/faceDirection farmer 3/move farmer 0 -1 3/move farmer -1 0 2/pause 2000/shake Emily 2000/pause 1500/speak Emily \"Heh... it's chilly out here...$4 / 嘿嘿…这里很冷……$4\"/pause 1000/faceDirection Emily 1/pause 500/faceDirection Emily 2/pause 500/animate Emily false true 250 52 53/pause 250/playSound dwop/positionOffset Emily 4 0/pause 250/pause 250/playSound dwop/positionOffset Emily 4 0/pause 250/pause 250/playSound dwop/positionOffset Emily 4 0/pause 250/pause 250/playSound dwop/positionOffset Emily 4 0/pause 250/pause 250/playSound dwop/positionOffset Emily 4 0/pause 250/pause 250/playSound dwop/positionOffset Emily 4 0/pause 250/pause 250/playSound dwop/positionOffset Emily 4 0/pause 250/pause 250/playSound dwop/positionOffset Emily 4 0/pause 250/stopAnimation Emily/pause 3000/showFrame Emily 55/pause 1000/eyes 1 -8500/pause 2000/emote farmer 32/pause 500/pause 1000/playSound leafrustle/pause 2000/addTemporaryActor Bear 32 32 23 4 2 true character/playSound leafrustle/pause 1000/move Bear 0 7 2/pause 1000/animate Bear false true 500 16 17/pause 500/playSound rabbit/pause 1000/playSound rabbit/pause 500/stopAnimation Bear/pause 1000/shake Bear 1000/playSound grunt/faceDirection farmer 3 true/faceDirection Emily 3 true/pause 1200/showFrame Emily 26/showFrame farmer 0/faceDirection farmer 2 true/showFrame farmer 94/jump Emily/jump farmer/pause 100/positionOffset Emily -4 0/pause 100/positionOffset Emily -4 0/pause 100/positionOffset Emily -4 0/pause 100/positionOffset Emily -4 0/pause 100/positionOffset Emily -4 0/pause 100/jump Bear/positionOffset Emily -4 0/pause 400/speed Emily 4/speed farmer 4/move Emily 0 -1 0/warp Emily -1000 -1000/playSound Ship/move farmer 0 -1 0/warp farmer -1000 -1000/playSound Ship/specificTemporarySprite shakeTent/pause 1000/specificTemporarySprite stopShakeTent/pause 1000/move Bear 0 1 2/pause 500/animate Bear false true 500 16 17/pause 500/playSound rabbit/pause 1000/playSound rabbit/pause 500/stopAnimation Bear/pause 500/faceDirection Bear 1/pause 1000/playSound grunt/shake Bear 500/pause 700/move Bear -4 0 2/move Bear 0 3 2/move Bear -3 0 3/warp Bear -1000 -1000/playSound leafrustle/pause 1000/speak Emily \"A bear! I hope he's not hungry... $6 / 一只熊！我希望他不饿……$6\"/pause 1000/specificTemporarySprite shakeTent/playSound grassyStep/pause 500/specificTemporarySprite stopShakeTent/pause 500/specificTemporarySprite shakeTent/playSound grassyStep/pause 500/specificTemporarySprite stopShakeTent/pause 500/speak Emily \"Oh... the other sleeping bag is still outside...$u / 哦……另一个睡袋还在外面……$u#$b#No way am I going back out there!$6 / 我没有办法回到那里去！$6\"/pause 2000/speak Emily \"Um.. @? You don't mind sharing a sleeping bag with me, do you?$4 / 嗯…@？你不介意和我共用一个睡袋吧，是吗？$4\"/pause 2000/specificTemporarySprite shakeTent/playSound grassyStep/pause 500/specificTemporarySprite stopShakeTent/pause 500/specificTemporarySprite shakeTent/playSound grassyStep/pause 500/specificTemporarySprite stopShakeTent/pause 500/specificTemporarySprite shakeTent/playSound grassyStep/pause 500/specificTemporarySprite stopShakeTent/pause 1200/specificTemporarySprite shakeTent/playSound grassyStep/pause 500/specificTemporarySprite stopShakeTent/pause 1000/playSound woodyHit/pause 3500/globalFade/viewport -2000 -2000/pause 1000/mail EmilyDoneCamping/end newDay",
        "2120303/S 23/i 724/t 600 1900": "nightTime/-1000 -1000/farmer 25 17 3/removeQuest 29/removeItem 724/skippable/addTemporaryActor Bear 32 32 11 17 2 true character/faceDirection Bear 1/viewport 11 17 clamp true/move farmer -6 0 3/pause 1000/startJittering/emote farmer 28/pause 1000/stopJittering/pause 500/animate Bear false true 500 16 17/pause 500/playSound rabbit/pause 1000/playSound rabbit/pause 500/stopAnimation Bear/speak Bear \"That smell... come closer...$2 / 那个味道是……靠近点……$2\"/pause 1000/move farmer -5 0 3/pause 1000/faceDirection Bear 2/pause 1000/speak Bear \"Heh... It's not every day I get to speak to a human. Looks like you've got a little 'forest magic' in you...$3 / 嘿……我可不是经常能跟人类说上话的。你似乎会一点“森林魔法”……$3\"/pause 100/jump Bear/pause 1000/faceDirection Bear 1/speak Bear \"Now... about my note... Did you bring the good stuff? / 现在……关于我的纸条……你带那个好东西来了吗？\"/pause 1000/animate farmer true true 100 35/playSound coin/addObject 13 17 724/pause 500/animate Bear false true 500 16 17/pause 500/stopAnimation farmer/playSound rabbit/pause 1000/playSound rabbit/pause 500/stopAnimation Bear/shake Bear 2000/pause 500/removeTemporarySprites/speak Bear \"HOoOoOoooh... that smell... this is really sweet stuff!$h / 呜噢噢噢噢噢噢噢……那个气味……肯定十分甜！$h#$b#...it's my favorite sauce... it makes me very happy.$h / ……这是我的最爱……我非常开心。$h\"/pause 1000/emote Bear 20/animate Bear false true 200 4 5 6 7/pause 50/positionOffset Bear 4 0/pause 100/positionOffset Bear 4 0/pause 100/positionOffset Bear 4 0/pause 100/positionOffset Bear 4 0/pause 100/positionOffset Bear 4 0/pause 100/positionOffset Bear 4 0/pause 100/positionOffset Bear 4 0/pause 100/positionOffset Bear 4 0/pause 100/positionOffset Bear 4 0/pause 100/positionOffset Bear 4 0/pause 100/positionOffset Bear 4 0/pause 100/positionOffset Bear 4 0/pause 100/positionOffset Bear 4 0/pause 100/positionOffset Bear 4 0/pause 100/positionOffset Bear 4 0/pause 100/positionOffset Bear 4 0/stopAnimation Bear/pause 500/playSound dwop/animate farmer true true 100 6/pause 100/positionOffset farmer 2 0/playSound dwop/animate farmer true true 100 7/pause 100/positionOffset farmer 2 0/playSound dwop/animate farmer true true 100 6/pause 100/positionOffset farmer 2 0/playSound dwop/animate farmer true true 100 7/pause 100/positionOffset farmer 2 0/playSound dwop/animate farmer true true 100 6/pause 100/positionOffset farmer 2 0/playSound dwop/animate farmer true true 100 7/pause 100/positionOffset farmer 2 0/playSound dwop/animate farmer true true 100 6/pause 100/positionOffset farmer 2 0/playSound dwop/animate farmer true true 100 7/pause 100/positionOffset farmer 2 0/stopAnimation farmer/pause 1000/speak Bear \"...You've made a friend today, @. / ……你今天结识了一个朋友，@。\"/pause 1000/animate Bear false true 200 4 5 6 7/pause 50/positionOffset Bear 4 0/pause 100/positionOffset Bear 4 0/pause 100/positionOffset Bear 4 0/pause 100/positionOffset Bear 4 0/pause 100/positionOffset Bear 4 0/pause 100/positionOffset Bear 4 0/pause 100/positionOffset Bear 4 0/stopAnimation Bear/pause 250/playSound dwop/animate farmer true true 100 6/pause 100/positionOffset farmer 2 0/playSound dwop/animate farmer true true 100 7/pause 100/positionOffset farmer 2 0/playSound dwop/animate farmer true true 100 6/pause 100/positionOffset farmer 2 0/playSound dwop/animate farmer true true 100 7/pause 100/positionOffset farmer 2 0/playSound dwop/animate farmer true true 100 6/pause 100/positionOffset farmer 2 0/playSound dwop/animate farmer true true 100 7/pause 100/positionOffset farmer 2 0/playSound dwop/animate farmer true true 100 6/pause 100/positionOffset farmer 2 0/playSound dwop/animate farmer true true 100 7/pause 100/positionOffset farmer 2 0/stopAnimation farmer/pause 1000/speak Bear \"I've got something special I want to show you... / 我有个特别的东西想让你看看……\"/pause 500/animate Bear false true 400 8 9 10 11/pause 400/playSound grassyStep/pause 400/playSound grassyStep/pause 400/playSound grassyStep/pause 400/playSound grassyStep/pause 400/playSound grassyStep/pause 400/playSound grassyStep/pause 400/playSound grassyStep/pause 400/playSound grassyStep/pause 400/stopAnimation Bear/fade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 2000/message \"The bear left you with his special knowledge... / 那只熊把他的特殊知识留给了你……\"/pause 1000/playSound reward/message \"Salmonberries and Blackberries are now worth 3x the gold! / 美洲大树莓和黑莓的价格提高到了 3 倍！\"/end"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Festivals/spring13",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "name": "Egg Festival / 复活节",
        "afterEggHunt": "pause 100/playSound whistle/waitForOtherPlayers endContest/pause 1000/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/playMusic event1/loadActors MainEvent/warpFarmers 27 69 0 26 67 1 32 67 3 28 71 0 22 65 1 25 63 2 32 65 3 32 62 2 right 31 71 0/pause 1000/viewport 27 67 true/pause 2000/speak Lewis \"Wow, look at all these eggs!$h / 哇，看这些蛋蛋！$h#$b#Now if only I could get you kids to pick up litter this efficiently, we'd have the cleanest town this side of the Gem Sea! *chuckle*$h / 如果你们这些孩子捡垃圾也有这个效率的话，我们就是宝石之海这一带最干净的城市了！* 咯咯 *$h\"/pause 800/playMusic none/speak Lewis \"And now, the winner of this year's egg hunt... / 那么，今年彩蛋大寻宝的获胜者是……\"/playMusic none/pause 3000/cutscene eggHuntWinner/null/playMusic event1/pause 500/fork AbbyWin/move Lewis 0 1 2/speak Lewis \"Here's your prize! Enjoy. / 这是你的奖品！希望你会喜欢。\"/awardFestivalPrize/null/move Lewis 0 -1 0/speak Lewis \"Well, that's it for this year's Egg Festival. Thanks for coming, everyone! / 好了，今年的蛋蛋节就此结束。谢谢大家捧场！\"/pause 600/viewport move 1 0 5000/pause 2000/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/waitForOtherPlayers festivalEnd/end",
        "AbbyWin": "pause 100/jump Abigail/faceDirection Vincent 3/pause 800/move Abigail 0 -1 0/faceDirection Vincent 0/speak Lewis \"Here's your prize, Abigail. Enjoy! / 这是你的奖品，阿比盖尔。希望你会喜欢！\"/pause 500/move Abigail 0 -1 0/playSound coin/pause 400/move Abigail 0 2 0/faceDirection Lewis 0/speak Lewis \"Well, that's it for this year's Egg Festival. Thanks for coming, everyone! / 好了，今年的蛋蛋节就此结束。谢谢大家捧场！\"/pause 1000/viewport move 1 -1 5000/pause 2000/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/waitForOtherPlayers festivalEnd/end",
        "mainEvent": "pause 500/playMusic none/pause 500/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/loadActors MainEvent/warpFarmers 27 69 0 27 67 1 32 67 3 28 71 0 26 71 0 25 63 2 32 63 2 34 63 2 left 33 71 0/pause 1000/viewport 27 67 true unfreeze/pause 2000/speak Lewis \"It's time for the highlight of today's festivities... The Annual Spring Egg Hunt!$h / 是时候开始今日庆典的压轴节目……年度春季彩蛋大寻宝了！$h\"/pause 100/jump Jas/jump Vincent/pause 1000/speak Lewis \"Calm down now, kiddos. You're going to need all your energy if you hope to find the most eggs and take home the exclusive prize. / 孩子们，别那么激动。节省点力气以便待会儿多找点彩蛋吧。\"/pause 100/faceDirection Vincent 3 true/faceDirection Jas 1 true/pause 1000/faceDirection Vincent 0 true/faceDirection Jas 0/pause 800/faceDirection Lewis 3/faceDirection Lewis 2/faceDirection Lewis 1/faceDirection Lewis 2/pause 800/speak Lewis \"Now... Is everyone ready? / 那么……大家都准备好了吗？\"/pause 1000/waitForOtherPlayers startContest/jump Lewis/pause 1000/speak Lewis \"Let the egg hunt begin!$h / 彩蛋大寻宝正式开始！$h\"/advancedMove Maru false -2 0 0 6 -9 0 0 -2 -9 0 0 -1 2 0 0 -12 6 0 0 -7 3 0/advancedMove Abigail false 0 21 -20 0 0 3 7 0 0 -15 -9 0 9 0 0 18/advancedMove Jas false 0 12 8 0 0 10 3 0 0 4 14 0 0 -20 -6 0 0 3/advancedMove Sam false 4 0 0 -4 2 0 0 -4 12 0 0 -6 19 0 0 20 0 -20 0 20/advancedMove Vincent false 0 3 24 0 0 21 9 0 0 4 -20 0 20 0 -20 0/advancedMove Leo false 0 -10 -1 0 0 -3 -6 0 0 -2 -3 0 0 -3 -1 0 0 20 -5 0 0 -10 -2 0/playSound whistle/playMusic tickTock/playerControl eggHunt",
        "afterEggHunt_y2": "pause 100/playSound whistle/waitForOtherPlayers endContest/pause 1000/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/playMusic event1/loadActors MainEvent/warpFarmers 29 70 0 26 68 1 27 70 0 33 68 3 33 70 3 30 71 0 29 72 0 27 72 0 right 34 70 3/pause 1000/positionOffset Demetrius 5 -10/positionOffset Jodi 5 -8/positionOffset Marnie -12 10/positionOffset Shane -6 -6/viewport 29 69 true/pause 2000/speak Lewis \"Wow, look at all these eggs!$h / 哇，这么多彩蛋！$h#$b#Now if only I could get you kids to pick up litter this efficiently, we'd have the cleanest town this side of the Gem Sea! *chuckle*$h / 如果你们这些年轻人捡垃圾也有这个效率的话，我们就是宝石海这一侧最干净的小镇了！哈哈。$h\"/pause 800/playMusic none/speak Lewis \"And now, the winner of this year's egg hunt... / 好了，今年彩蛋寻宝的获胜者是……\"/playMusic none/pause 3000/cutscene eggHuntWinner/null/playMusic event1/pause 500/fork AbbyWin/move Lewis 0 1 2/speak Lewis \"Here's your prize! Enjoy. / 这是你的奖品！希望你会喜欢。\"/awardFestivalPrize/null/pause 300/faceDirection Lewis 1/faceDirection Lewis 0/move Lewis 0 -1 0/speak Lewis \"Well, that's it for this year's Egg Festival. Thanks for coming, everyone! / 今年的彩蛋节到此结束，谢谢大家捧场！\"/pause 600/viewport move 1 0 5000/pause 2000/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/waitForOtherPlayers festivalEnd/end",
        "mainEvent_y2": "pause 500/playMusic none/pause 500/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/loadActors MainEvent/warpFarmers 29 70 0 26 68 1 27 70 0 33 68 3 33 70 3 30 71 0 29 72 0 27 72 0 left 34 70 3/pause 1000/positionOffset Demetrius 5 -10/positionOffset Jodi 5 -8/positionOffset Marnie -12 10/positionOffset Shane -6 -6/viewport 29 69 true unfreeze/pause 2000/speak Lewis \"It's time for the highlight of today's festivities... The Annual Spring Egg Hunt!$h / 是时候开始今天庆典的压轴节目了……那就是一年一度的春季彩蛋寻宝！$h\"/pause 100/jump Jas/jump Vincent/pause 1000/speak Lewis \"Calm down now, kiddos. You're going to need all your energy if you hope to find the most eggs and take home the exclusive prize. / 孩子们，别那么激动，节省点力气，待会儿才能多找点彩蛋，拿到最终奖品。\"/pause 100/faceDirection Vincent 1 true/faceDirection Jas 3 true/pause 1000/faceDirection Vincent 0 true/faceDirection Jas 0/pause 800/faceDirection Lewis 3/pause 100/faceDirection Lewis 2/pause 125/faceDirection Lewis 1/pause 100/faceDirection Lewis 2/pause 800/speak Lewis \"Now... Is everyone ready? / 行了……大家都准备好了吗？\"/pause 1000/waitForOtherPlayers startContest/jump Lewis/pause 1000/speak Lewis \"Let the egg hunt begin!$h / 彩蛋寻宝正式开始！$h\"/advancedMove Abigail false -2 0 0 -3 -7 0 0 -2 -2 0 0 -5 1 0 0 -4 -3 0 0 5 -2 0 0 14 54 0/advancedMove Sam false 0 11 26 0 0 15 -14 0 0 -5 -9 0 0 -9 6 0 0 8 -4 0/advancedMove Jas false 0 1 3 0 0 1 15 0 0 -8 7 0 0 9 -7 0 0 7 -20 0 0 10 -21 0/advancedMove Vincent false 4 300 1 400 1 0 0 1 3 0 0 1 15 0 0 -8 7 0 0 9 -7 0 0 7 -20 0 0 10 -20 0/advancedMove Maru false 0 -4 2 0 0 -3 3 0 0 -2 12 0 0 -6 19 0 0 19 -31 0 0 -10/advancedMove Leo false 0 2 -2 0 0 1 -3 0 0 1 -5 0 0 2 22 0 0 -4 30 0 0 -18 -15 0/advancedMove Haley true 3 7000 2 5000/advancedMove Gus true 1 5500 0 -2 4 400 1 7000 2 400 0 2 2 400 1 1000/playSound whistle/playMusic tickTock/playerControl eggHunt",
        "Abigail_spouse": "Go away, we're adversaries until the egg hunt is over!$h / 走开，在寻宝活动结束前，我们是竞争对手！$h",
        "Leah_spouse": "I never had many friends in town, so these events are always kind of boring for me. I enjoy the buffet, though. / 我在城里没什么朋友，所以这些活动对我来说没有意义。不过我很喜欢活动准备的自助餐。",
        "Maru_spouse": "I'm just catching up with Penny. Have you had your fill of eggs? / 我才刚赶上潘妮。你的进度如何？",
        "Penny_spouse": "Maru's trying to convince me to eat a deviled egg. I'm just not sure I can stomach it... / 玛鲁试图说服我吃一个辣椒粉蛋。我不觉得我能咽得下……",
        "Haley_spouse": "I was going to eat some eggs, but then I remembered I'm on a spring diet. / 我本来是打算跟鸡蛋展开大作战的，但突然想起最近在减肥。",
        "Sebastian_spouse": "I'll be rooting for you in the egg hunt.$h / 我看好你会赢得彩蛋寻宝。加油。$h",
        "Sam_spouse": "The gang's just the same as always. Are you having a good time? / 还是往年的那班人参与。你玩得开心不？",
        "Alex_spouse": "Ungh... I think I ate a dozen too many hard boiled eggs...$s / 呜呃……我好像吃太多水煮蛋了……$s",
        "Harvey_spouse": "How is everyone doing? I'm just taking a break for a little while. I'm looking forward to seeing you in the egg hunt! / 大家的表现如何？我在休息一会儿。期待在彩蛋寻宝中跟你一决高下！",
        "Elliott_spouse": "I enjoy seeing you so relaxed, my dear.$h / 很高兴见到你这么快乐，亲爱的。$h",
        "Abigail": "Searching for eggs is like going on a treasure hunt.$h / 寻找彩蛋就犹如寻找宝藏。$h",
        "Robin": "Spring is a busy time of year... so it's nice to have a day off to catch up with friends. / 春季是全年最繁忙的季节……能休息一天和朋友聚聚感觉真不错。",
        "Demetrius": "Egg... what a strange thing to eat. / 鸡蛋……不明白为什么那么多人喜欢吃。",
        "Maru": "I always look forward to these gatherings... it makes the valley feel like a real community. / 我一直很喜欢这种聚会……让星露谷变得不会那么死气沉沉。",
        "Sebastian": "We used to do a rotten egg toss... / 我们以前有个扔臭鸡蛋环节……#$b#Mayor Lewis put an end to that pretty quick. / 不过很快就让刘易斯镇长给禁止了。",
        "Linus": "No one really talks to me... I just come for the deviled eggs. / 很少人理会我……我只是为了吃辣椒粉蛋而来的。",
        "Pierre": "Hey! How'd you get back here?$u / 咦！你怎么跑来这里了？$u#$b#Don't touch anything. / 不要乱碰任何东西。",
        "Caroline": "Abby's always loved the egg hunt, ever since she was a tiny girl. / 阿比盖尔打从小时候就很喜欢彩蛋大寻宝。",
        "Alex": "I try to eat at least three eggs every day. / 我在努力每天吃至少三个鸡蛋。#$e#I need that protein for my legs. / 我的腿需要更多蛋白质。",
        "George": "What's everyone so happy about? Hmmph... / 大家怎么都那么兴致勃勃的？呃……#$b#Eggs... why eggs? / 吃鸡蛋……不是吧？",
        "Evelyn": "This festival has been a tradition for as long as I can remember. / 从我小时候开始这个节日就成了镇上不可分割的传统。#$b#Tradition connects us with both the past and the future... it's comforting. / 传统把我们的过去与未来联系在一起……想想就有点小安慰。",
        "Lewis": "Enjoying yourself, @?$h / 玩得开心吗，@？$h",
        "Clint": "Is there any more food?$s / 还有更多食物不？$s",
        "Penny": "The children have been looking forward to this festival for weeks. / 孩子们盼着过节盼了好几个礼拜了。",
        "Pam": "Hehe... I put something nice into the punch.$h / 哈哈……我在潘趣酒里加了料。$h#$e#Shhh... that's just between you and me, kid. / 嘘……别告诉其他人哦，小伙子。",
        "Emily": "I've been up since dawn coloring eggs... it's always my favorite part of the season.$h / 我天一亮就爬起来给鸡蛋上色了……这是我整个季节最期待的一天。$h",
        "Haley": "This festival is alright... but what I'm really looking forward to is the Flower Dance. / 这个节日还不错……但我最喜欢的是花舞节。",
        "Jodi": "Vincent loves this festival... it's a joy to see him so happy. / 文森特很喜欢这个节日……看到他那么高兴我也很开心。",
        "Kent": "I'm not a big fan of eggs, to tell you the truth. / 讲真，我不是很喜欢吃鸡蛋。",
        "Marlon": "Even with my bad leg, I never miss a town festival. / 哪怕我行动不方便，镇上的节日我也一次不落。",
        "Sam": "*sniff*... ub... my doze... allergies...$s / *吸气* ……噢……我的鼻子……过敏……$s",
        "Leah": "Mmmm... This fruit punch is unusually good.$h / 嗯……这杯水果潘趣酒真是妙极了。$h",
        "Shane": "Our hens have been working overtime to prepare for this festival. / 为了准备这次节目，我家的母鸡加班加点地下蛋。#$b#They deserve the best tonight... bowls full of sweet yellow corn!$h / 今晚我要犒劳它们大碗大碗的玉米谷粮！$h",
        "Marnie": "Welcome to the Egg Festival... compliments of my wonderful brood of hens. / 欢迎来到复活节……这个节日全靠我家母鸡下的蛋维持着。",
        "Elliott": "Taking breaks from work can make you more productive in the long run. / 从长远角度看工作时抽空休息一下能让你变得更有效率。",
        "Gus": "I hope everyone's enjoying the food... I've been cooking for days to get everything ready. / 希望大家吃得开心……这些食物花了我好几天的功夫。#$b#Fried eggs, boiled eggs, poached eggs, deviled eggs, scrambled eggs, chocolate eggs... you name it!$h / 煎蛋、水煮蛋、荷包蛋、辣椒粉蛋、炒蛋、巧克力蛋……应有尽有！$h",
        "Dwarf": "You say it's raining up above? *gasp* / 地面上下雨了？*喘气*#$e#Rain... it's almost mythical to us. Some of us live our entire lives without ever experiencing it. / 下雨……这是个很陌生的概念。我们大部分人一辈子都没经历过下雨。",
        "Wizard": "Hmm... And what about raw lizard egg sprinkled with blackened marrow? / 唔……那搭配黑骨髓的生蜥蜴蛋呢？",
        "Harvey": "Eggs definitely have a place in the well-balanced diet. / 鸡蛋是健康饮食的重要成分。#$e#Oops... I should take off my Doctor's hat for the time being.$11 / 哈哈，不好意思……我的医生职业病又犯了。$11",
        "Sandy": "I heard it's raining back home. Is that why you came here?$h / 听说家乡在下雨。你是为避雨才跑来这里的吗？$h#$e#I kind of miss the rain, actually...$s / 话说我有点怀念雨景了……$s",
        "Jas": "I hope I can find some eggs before Vincent takes them all...$s / 希望能赶在被文森特席卷一空前抢到一些鸡蛋……$s",
        "Vincent": "When does the egg hunt start?! I'm so excited!!$h / 彩蛋大寻宝什么时候开始啊？我好激动啊！！$h",
        "Willy": "Sometimes I'll hide an egg too well and no one finds it... / 有时候我把蛋藏得太好，搞得大家都找不到……#$b#Well, until summer rolls around. Then the hot air starts to bring out the rotten smell... Hehe. $h / 然后到夏季来临，热空气把鸡蛋的腐烂异味吹出来……那叫一个酸爽啊。 $h",
        "???": "Ah, the sewers are flowing quickly today. It'll get nice and humid in here... just how I like it. / 啊，今天下水道排水好快。这里将会变得十分潮湿……最喜欢这种天气了。",
        "Leo": "The idea of an egg hunt is a little bit weird... but I guess the eggs don't belong to any of my family members...$s / 总感觉彩蛋大寻宝这个主意有点奇怪……但我估计这些蛋也不会是我家族成员的蛋……$s#$b#Oh well, I'll join in anyway!$h / 嗯，行吧，我也去参加！$h",
        "Abigail_y2": "$y 'Do you think I'm too old to do the egg hunt?_Yes_Hmmph... you sound like my Mom!$a_No_Yeah, I guess so. If I'm still having fun, why stop?' / $y '你觉得我现在还去玩彩蛋寻宝是不是太幼稚了？_是的_唔……你这话说得跟我妈一样！$a_不会_哈，我也觉得。只要能玩得开心，那为什么不玩？'",
        "Robin_y2": "It feels great to be outside again after that long, cold winter, doesn't it? / 过了漫长的寒冬，能再出门感觉真舒服，是不是？",
        "Demetrius_y2": "Hey @, did you get a taste of my carp roe pie? / 嘿，@，你尝过我做的的鲤鱼籽派了吗？#$b#...What? It is the 'egg' festival, isn't it? / ……怎么？鱼籽不也是一种蛋吗？",
        "Maru_y2": "Think you'll win the egg hunt this year? / 你觉得今年的彩蛋寻宝你会赢吗？",
        "Sebastian_y2": "You know what? I kind of miss the winter... it's simpler, in a way. / 我有点怀念冬天了……某种意义上说，冬天更纯粹。",
        "Linus_y2": "I'll just slip in a little later and have some food. I'm eyeing that scrumptious looking pie! / 我一会儿就溜进去吃点东西。我很馋那个派，看起来很美味！",
        "Pierre_y2": "Trying to make a back-room deal, huh? Hah! I admire your gumption. / 嗯，想要做一笔幕后交易？哈！挺精明的嘛。",
        "Caroline_y2": "It may be a little boring, but these festivals are a good chance to connect with our neighbors. / 老生常谈——这些节日是与我们邻居交流的大好机会。",
        "Alex_y2": "I wonder what would happen to my arms and legs if I ate thirty eggs a day? / 我在想如果我一天吃 30 个鸡蛋，我的胳膊和腿会怎么样？",
        "George_y2": "Evelyn made eggs and leeks for breakfast, so I'm in a good mood.$h / 伊芙莉早餐做了鸡蛋和韭葱，所以我现在心情很好。$h",
        "Evelyn_y2": "$y 'Do you have hens on your farm?_Yes_Oh, good! I'm sure they lay the most delicious eggs...$h_No_Spring would be a great time to start raising chickens, don't you think?' / $y '你的农场里有母鸡吗？_有_哦，太好了！它们下的蛋肯定最好吃……$h_没有_春天可是开始养鸡的好时候，你觉得呢？'",
        "Clint_y2": "Oh no... *gulp*... It's mostly salad this year...$s / 嘶……哦不……今年怎么这么多沙拉……$s",
        "Penny_y2": "Hopefully Vincent will be able to find an egg this year...  / 希望文森特今年能找到一颗彩蛋……#$b#It would be good for him to feel like he's a contender. / 能参与到竞赛的紧张感中去对他来说是件好事。",
        "Pam_y2": "Hey... If you're gonna feed me eggs, I'm gonna need some hot sauce, kid! / 嘿……孩子，如果你要让我吃鸡蛋的话，我还要配一点辣酱！",
        "Emily_y2": "This year I sewed little pants and hats for some of the eggs. They look adorable!$h / 今年，我给几个彩蛋缝了小裤子和小帽子。它们看起来很可爱！$h",
        "Haley_y2": "Oh! I still need to get my photo taken at the bunny stand. Does my hair look okay? / 啊！我还得在兔子摊前照个相。我的头发看起来没问题吧？",
        "Jodi_y2": "Kent always seems a little antsy during big gatherings like this... / 肯特在这样的大聚会上总是显得有点烦躁……",
        "Marlon_y2": "Have you ever hunted for slime eggs? Now there's a true challenge... / 你抓到过史莱姆蛋吗？这就是真正的挑战了……",
        "Leah_y2": "Hmm... The punch isn't as good as last year. It's missing something! / 唔……潘趣酒没有去年的好了。好像缺了点什么东西！",
        "Shane_y2": "Some of these eggs were laid just this morning. See? They're still warm! / 有些蛋是今天早上刚下的。感受到了吗？它们还很暖和！",
        "Marnie_y2": "Hens lay the eggs, but roosters play an important role, too... they protect the hens and prevent them from fighting with each other! / 母鸡下蛋，但公鸡也扮演着重要的角色……它们保护母鸡，防止母鸡互相打架！#$b#That means happier hens and better eggs...$h / 这样就有更快乐的母鸡和质量更好的蛋……$h",
        "Elliott_y2": "Be careful you don't accidentally take a raven's egg. They'll hold a grudge against you for the rest of their days! / 当心别误拿了乌鸦蛋。它们的余生都会对你怀恨在心！",
        "Gus_y2": "Shh... don't tell anyone, but I tried something different this year... Duck eggs in the custard!$h / 嘘……别告诉其他人——我今年打算做点不同的东西……用鸭蛋做蛋奶冻！$h",
        "Harvey_y2": "Eggs are fine, but I'd advise against eating thirty per day! / 鸡蛋有益，但我建议不要一天吃三十个！",
        "Jas_y2": "I'm going to try my best to win this year! / 今年我要尽全力去赢！",
        "Vincent_y2": "I want to live inside a big egg! / 我想住在一个超大的蛋里！",
        "Willy_y2": "Aye... on rainy days, you'll find catfish in these waters. They're a challenging catch, but well worth the effort! / 对……在雨天，你可以在水里找到鲶鱼。它们很难捉到，但值得你去努力！"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Festivals/spring24",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "name": "Flower Dance / 花舞节",
        "mainEvent": "pause 500/playMusic none/pause 500/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/loadActors MainEvent/warpFarmers 14 30 0 3 22 1 3 26 1 7 31 0 12 31 0 18 31 0 25 29 3 right 24 25 3/warp Girls 9 24/warp Guys 9 27/showFrame Girls 40/showFrame Guys 44/viewport 14 25 clamp true/pause 2000/playMusic FlowerDance/pause 600/animate Girls false true 600 43 41 43 42/animate Guys false true 600 44 45/pause 9600/animate Girls false true 600 46 47/animate Guys false true 300 46 47/positionOffset Guys 0 -2/pause 300/positionOffset Guys 0 -2/pause 300/positionOffset Guys 0 -2/pause 300/positionOffset Guys 0 -2/pause 300/positionOffset Guys 0 -2/pause 300/positionOffset Guys 0 -2/pause 300/positionOffset Guys 0 -2/pause 300/positionOffset Guys 0 -2/pause 300/positionOffset Guys 0 -2/pause 300/positionOffset Guys 0 -2/pause 300/positionOffset Guys 0 -2/pause 300/positionOffset Guys 0 -2/pause 300/positionOffset Guys 0 -2/pause 300/positionOffset Guys 0 -2/pause 300/positionOffset Guys 0 -2/pause 300/positionOffset Guys 0 -2/pause 300/positionOffset Guys 0 -2/pause 300/positionOffset Guys 0 -2/pause 300/positionOffset Guys 0 -2/pause 300/positionOffset Guys 0 -2/pause 300/positionOffset Guys 0 -2/pause 300/positionOffset Guys 0 -2/pause 300/positionOffset Guys 0 -2/pause 300/positionOffset Guys 0 -2/pause 300/positionOffset Guys 0 -2/pause 300/positionOffset Guys 0 -2/pause 300/positionOffset Guys 0 -2/pause 300/positionOffset Guys 0 -2/animate Girls false true 600 43 41 43 42/animate Guys false true 600 44 45/pause 7600/stopAnimation Girls/stopAnimation Guys/pause 3000/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/message \"That was fun! Time to go home... / 真有趣！该回家了……\"/waitForOtherPlayers festivalEnd/end",
        "Abigail": "I really hate dancing in front of everyone... It's so embarrassing. / 我最讨厌在大家面前跳舞……真的好尴尬。#$e#Mom makes me do it.$u / 都是妈妈逼我的。$u",
        "Robin": "Ahh... The air smells so sweet with all these flowers.$h / 啊……啊……这些花朵让空气都变得甜蜜起来了。$h",
        "Demetrius": "These springtime dances can be traced back to ancient fertility rituals. / 春季舞会可以追溯到远古时期的丰饶仪式。#$e#Hey... You should know about this stuff, farmer. / 嘿……你这个农夫应该对这些事情很懂才对啊。",
        "Maru": "I like dancing, but this one is a little stilted. The old timers really love it, though. / 我喜欢跳舞，但这种舞蹈过于生硬，不合我口味。不过老一代的人都很喜欢。",
        "Sebastian": "Ugh... / 啊……",
        "Linus": "Oh, hello there. It's nice of you to talk to me. / 哦，你好。很高兴你来陪我聊天。#$b#Spring is almost over... what a shame. / 春天就快结束了……有点伤感。",
        "Pierre": "What! How'd you get back here?$u / 哟！你怎么又回来了？$u#$b#Don't touch anything. / 不要碰任何东西。",
        "Caroline": "I wish Pierre would spend this time with the family...$s / 真希望此时此刻皮埃尔能陪伴自己的家人……$s",
        "Alex": "I'm just enjoying the scenery... hehe. / 我在欣赏这美景呢……嘿嘿。",
        "George": "Flowers? I can hardly see them. / 花？我什么花都看不见。#$e#It's too bright out here! / 这里太明亮了！",
        "Evelyn": "I've been working on these floral arrangements for a week. Do you like them? / 这些花卉我弄了一个星期了。好看不？",
        "Lewis": "If you'd like to dance with the other young people, you'll need to find a partner. / 要想跟其他年轻人跳舞，那你就得找个舞伴。",
        "Clint": "I wonder if Emily would dance with me? / 不知道艾米丽是否愿意跟我跳舞呢？",
        "Penny": "*gulp*... I'm nervous.$s / * 深呼吸 *……紧张紧张好紧张。$s",
        "Pam": "Now this is the life... Huh, kid? Sweet wine, a babbling brook, warm air... Did I mention wine? / 这才是生活嘛……对吧，小子？小桥美酒人家……咦，我说美酒来着吗？",
        "Emily": "Whoo... I'm stuffed. Hey, have you tried the red jelly yet? / 喔……好饱。嘿，你尝了红果冻吗？",
        "Haley": "I'm practicing my dance moves... It needs to be perfect. / 我在练习舞姿呢……必须要做到尽善尽美。#$e#I've been flower queen for the past 5 years and I'm not ready to step off the throne just yet! / 我已经连续五年蝉联花卉女王的头衔了，今年也不打算让贤！",
        "Jodi": "Are you going to be dancing today, @?$h / 你今天打算跳舞不，@？$h",
        "Kent": "This open field... it makes me nervous. / 这么大的场合……好紧张啊。#$e#*whisper* Happy thoughts, Kent. Happy Thoughts. / *细语* 冷静冷静。我要冷静。",
        "Marlon": "Marnie looks lovely today... / 玛妮今天好美呀……",
        "Sam": "You know what? I admit it... I really like flowers! / 好吧，我承认……我真的很喜欢花朵！",
        "Leah": "Hi @. Glad to see you here.$h / 嗨，@。你也来啦。$h",
        "Shane": "Mmm... excellent sauce. *slurp* / 咂砸……顶级的酱料啊。*咕噜*#$e#Ah, this green stuff is spicy! *munch* / 嗯，这绿色的玩意好辣！* 咀嚼 *#$b#*crunch* ...ow.$s / *咂巴嘴* ……哇塞。$s",
        "Marnie": "*sigh*... Love is in the air... And I'm still single.$s / *唉*……大家都成双成对……凄凄惨惨戚戚。$s",
        "Elliott": "I wore my best shirt for the dance... This sort of thing doesn't happen very often! / 我穿着最炫酷的衣服来参加舞会……这种事情一年就一次呢！",
        "Gus": "Frog season is really starting to pick up. / 属于青蛙的季节就要到了。",
        "Dwarf": "You say it's raining up above? *gasp* / 地面上下雨了？*喘气*#$e#Rain... It's almost mythical to us. Some of us live our entire lives without ever experiencing it. / 下雨……这是个很陌生的概念。我们大部分人一辈子都没经历过下雨。",
        "Wizard": "You shouldn't be up here. / 你不该来。",
        "Harvey": "I'm working up the courage to ask someone to dance with me.$11 / 我在累积着勇气去邀人共舞。$11",
        "Sandy": "I heard it's raining back home. Is that why you came here?$h / 听说家乡在下雨。你是为避雨才跑来这里的吗？$h#$e#I kind of miss the rain, actually...$s / 话说我有点怀念雨景了……$s",
        "Jas": "Some day, I'm going to be the flower queen! / 总有一天，我会成为花卉女王的！",
        "Vincent": "That's not fair... Why can't I be the flower queen? / 这不公平……为什么不能让我成为花卉女王？",
        "Willy": "I should've brought my fishing pole. / 早知道把鱼竿也带上。",
        "Leo": "The flowers here are nice, but they aren't as colorful as back home!$h / 这里的花很漂亮，但没有我家的花那么鲜艳多彩！$h#$e#I wonder if I'll ever have to get up there and dance...$u / 不知道我是不是需要去花丛里跳支舞……$u",
        "Abigail_spouse_y2": "We don't have to dance if you don't want to!$1 / 如果你不想跳，我们就不跳了！$1",
        "Penny_spouse_y2": "I could imagine us moving to a spot like this, someday.$h / 如果有一天能搬到这样的地方也挺好的。$h",
        "Leah_spouse_y2": "We should go hiking in these woods someday! I bet there's mushrooms... / 我们哪天到森林里旅行一趟吧！肯定会有很多蘑菇……",
        "Haley_spouse_y2": "Today is the big day! We'll be the centerpiece of the whole dance!$1 / 今天是个重要的日子！我们会成为整场舞会的焦点！$1",
        "Maru_spouse_y2": "I didn't practice much beforehand but I'll give it my best for the both of us.$0 / 我没提前练习很多，不过我会尽力的，为了咱们俩。$0",
        "Emily_spouse_y2": "Hey, I was wondering what you were up to!$0 / 哎，你最近在忙什么呀！$0",
        "Harvey_spouse_y2": "I wore my best tie for the occasion.$4 / 为了参加舞会，我系了我最好的领带。$4",
        "Alex_spouse_y2": "Hey, I'm feeling pretty good about today. We'll do great during the ceremony... just follow my lead.$0 / 哎，我今天特别有信心，我们肯定能跳得很好……跟着我一起跳就行了。$0",
        "Sam_spouse_y2": "Whoa, you look really great today.$0 / 哇，你今天真好看。$0",
        "Sebastian_spouse_y2": "You're the only reason I came all the way out here...$1 / 我大老远到这里来，就是为了和你一起……$1",
        "Elliott_spouse_y2": "May I have this dance?$4 / 我可以邀请你跳舞吗？$4",
        "Shane_spouse_y2": "*burp* I might've eaten too much to dance... sorry.$0 / 嗝！我吃太多了，还能不能跳舞啊……对不起。$0",
        "Abigail_y2": "They should make the seniors dance this year. I bet they'd love it! / 今年应该让老人们跳舞的，他们肯定很乐意！",
        "Robin_y2": "Is that the smell of flowers? Or is it Caroline's perfume?$0 / 是花香吗？还是卡洛琳喷了香水？$0",
        "Demetrius_y2": "Gatherings like this give a sense of identity to our community. / 这样的聚会可以促进我们小镇的认同感。#$b#Or as my wife says... 'it makes the town lively'! / 用我老婆的话就是……“会让小镇充满活力！”",
        "Maru_y2": "It can be a little nerve-racking to ask someone to dance with you.$0 / 邀请别人一起跳舞可能会有点紧张的。$0",
        "Sebastian_y2": "I didn't come here by choice.$0 / 我来这里不是自愿的。$0",
        "Linus_y2": "Did you have a successful salmonberry harvest?$0 / 你采到的美洲大树莓多不多？$0#$b#I picked enough to make a sweet and tangy jelly! I brought some today for everyone to taste.$1 / 我采到了很多，还做了酸甜的果冻！今天我带来给大家尝尝。$1",
        "Pierre_y2": "Hey, you shouldn't be back here!$3 / 喂，你在这里做什么！$3#$e#Well, if you're sticking around... mind manning the booth for a while? I want to taste Linus' sweet and tangy jelly. / 呃，如果你要待在这里的话……能不能帮我看一会儿摊子？我想去尝一尝莱纳斯做的酸甜果冻。#$e#I'm joking, I can't bear to be away from the register...$2 / 跟你开玩笑的，我怎么可能离开收银台……$2",
        "Caroline_y2": "I'd ask my husband to dance, but he doesn't really know how.$0 / 我想邀请我老公跳舞，可惜他不怎么会跳。$0",
        "Alex_y2": "The key to dancing is to have confidence.$1 / 跳舞的秘诀就是自信。$1",
        "George_y2": "Flowers? More like bumblebee magnets. Hmph. Can't smell much anyway.$0 / 花有什么好的，全是大黄蜂围在那里。哼，反正我也闻不到什么味道了。$0",
        "Evelyn_y2": "I used to visit this spot when I was younger. It hasn't changed much over the years.$0 / 我年轻的时候经常来这里，这么多年过去了也没什么变化。$0",
        "Lewis_y2": "Good afternoon, @. The weather for today's festivities couldn't be more perfect.$0 / @，下午好。今天天气太好了，正适合举办庆祝活动。$0#$b#Come talk to me when you're ready to start the ceremony.$0 / 等你准备好开始就来找我。$0",
        "Clint_y2": "*sigh* Everyone is partnered up... and here I am alone, once again...$2 / 唉，大家都有舞伴了……我又是一个人……$2#$e#Ah well... I'll just drown my sorrows with some of that sweet and tangy jelly. / 好吧，我大概只好吃酸甜果冻来消愁了。",
        "Penny_y2": "Vincent asked me to dance with him. Isn't that cute?$0 / 文森特来邀请我一起跳舞，他很可爱吧？$0",
        "Pam_y2": "The red jelly wafting in the wind looks like it's dancing!$1 / 风中飘散着红色果冻，就像在跳舞一样！$1#$e#Heh... Maybe that's just the wine speaking.$0 / 呃……我大概是喝醉了吧。$0",
        "Emily_y2": "Oh, hey! This year I'm giving my sister competition for the flower queen title.$0 / 啊，你好！今年我要跟我妹妹竞争花舞女王的称号。$0#$b#I've been working on my choreography!$1 / 我一直在打磨我的编舞！$1",
        "Haley_y2": "One, two, three... one, two, three... Oh, hi. I'm a little busy.$0 / 一二三……二二三……啊，你好。我现在有点忙。$0",
        "Jodi_y2": "I have special earrings I only wear once a year for this event.$0 / 我有一对特别的耳环，只有每年这个活动才戴。$0#$e#They're little daffodils... see?$h / 是小小的黄水仙的图案……看到了吗？$h",
        "Kent_y2": "Do you ever wonder... why do we find flowers beautiful? / 你有没有想过……为什么我们会觉得花很漂亮？#$e#If Jodi and I ever have a daughter, maybe we'll name her after a flower.$h / 如果乔迪和我生了女儿的话，我们可能会用花的名字给她取名。$h",
        "Marlon_y2": "Hmm. Thought I saw something moving across the water.$0 / 唔，我好像看到有什么东西在水上掠过去了。$0",
        "Sam_y2": "*sniff* I'd enjoy this get-together more if it wasn't for my allergies. I'll just have to suck it up!$0 / 阿嚏……要不是我过敏的话，肯定能玩得很痛快。现在只好忍着了！$0",
        "Leah_y2": "I really feel connected with nature this far away from town.$0 / 在这里远离小镇，我感觉自己跟大自然更亲近了。$0",
        "Shane_y2": "I couldn't find any clean shirts so this one has to do.$0 / 我没找到干净的上衣，就只好穿这件了。$0",
        "Marnie_y2": "This open field is perfect grazing land for livestock, wouldn't you agree?$0 / 这个地方很开阔，非常适合放牧，你说是不是？$0#$e#Psst... I think Lewis is going to ask me to dance with him!$1 / 悄悄跟你说……我感觉刘易斯会邀请我跳舞！$1",
        "Elliott_y2": "To dance among a whimsical backdrop of flowers is an uplifting experience.$1 / 在一片梦幻的花丛中跳舞，真是引人入胜。$1",
        "Gus_y2": "Have you tried the dandelion salad? I prepared it fresh right here!$0 / 你尝过蒲公英沙拉吗？这是我就地取材做的！$0",
        "Wizard_y2": "Hmm? How did you climb up here?$0 / 嗯？你怎么爬上来的？$0",
        "Harvey_y2": "If you spend some time pondering the hardships of life, it can put things into perspective.$0 / 如果你花点时间琢磨一下生活的艰辛，就能更客观地看待事物。$0#$b#Suddenly, dancing in front of the whole town in an ill-fitting suit doesn't seem so bad!$h / 这么一想，穿着不合身的西装在全镇人面前跳舞好像也没那么糟糕了！$h",
        "Jas_y2": "*giggle* Am I doing it right?$1 / 嘻嘻……我这样对不对？$1",
        "Vincent_y2": "If there's a flower queen... there must be a flower king!$0 / 如果有花舞女王……那肯定也有花舞男王！$0",
        "Willy_y2": "Aye, these waters be teeming with big fish. Shame I didn't bring me rod!$0 / 好哇，这水里都是大鱼，可惜我没带鱼竿！$0",
        "Leo_y2": "You need a partner to participate in the dance? Does a bird count?$0 / 你跳舞需要舞伴吗？鸟儿可以当舞伴吗？$0"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Festivals/summer11",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "name": "Luau / 夏威夷宴会",
        "mainEvent": "pause 500/playMusic ocean/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/loadActors MainEvent/addTemporaryActor Governor 16 32 35 10 2/warpFarmers 33 19 0 32 19 0 40 19 0 28 9 1 42 9 3 37 19 0 38 19 0 34 19 0 right 36 6 2/viewport 35 12 true/pause 2000/faceDirection Lewis 3/pause 100/faceDirection Lewis 2/pause 100/faceDirection Lewis 1/pause 100/faceDirection Lewis 2/speak Lewis \"Well folks, it's time once again for the potluck ceremony. / 伙计们，又到了一年一度的百乐餐典礼。#$b#I trust that you all put high-quality ingredients in the pot this year. We don't want the governor to regret his visit to the valley! / 我相信你们都往锅里放了上好的材料。我们一定要让州长先生不虚此行啊！\"/pause 1000/faceDirection Lewis 3/pause 500/speak Lewis \"Well... Governor? Would you do us the honor of tasting the soup? / 嗯……州长？能有幸请您尝尝这汤么？\"/pause 500/speak Governor \"Of course! I've been looking forward to this all year. / 当然了！这一刻我期盼已久。\"/playMusic none/pause 500/move Governor 0 1 2/pause 1000/playSound dwop/showFrame Governor 8 true/pause 1000/animate Governor false false 200 8 8 9 10 11 11/pause 1100/playSound sipTea/pause 1000/playSound gulp/pause 500/showFrame Governor 8 true/animate Governor false false 200 11 10 9 8/pause 900/speak Governor \"...$h / ……$h\"/pause 300/cutscene governorTaste/null",
        "governorReaction6": "pause 1000/playMusic ocean/speak Governor \"Hmm... It's a bit tangy... but actually, the flavor is quite good! / 嗯……有点刺鼻……但实际上，味道非常好！\"/pause 600/emote Governor 8/speak Governor \"Just one minute... there's something in my bowl... what's this?$2 / 稍等一分钟……我的碗里有东西……这是什么？$2\"/pause 500/showFrame Governor 14/playSound slimeHit/jump Governor/pause 500/showFrame Lewis 24/jump Lewis/textAboveHead Lewis \"Whaaaat?! / 什……么？！\"/showFrame Emily 26/pause 1000/showFrame Marnie 16/jump Marnie/textAboveHead Marnie \"*gasp* / 嘶……\"/pause 1000/shake Governor 2000/emote Governor 12/pause 500/showFrame Emily 4/showFrame Marnie 8/speak Governor \"This... This is outrageous!$1 / 这个……这太离谱了！$1#$b#I've never been so insulted in all my life!$1 / 我一生中从未受过如此侮辱！$1\"/pause 600/showFrame Governor 13/playSound throw/specificTemporarySprite luauShorts/pause 500/jump Lewis/pause 1000/speak Governor \"Blech... my tongue is swelling up... I think I'm going to be sick.$u / 呸……我的舌头肿了……我感觉好恶心。$u\"/pause 400/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 1000/warp Governor -100 -100/playSound slimedead/faceDirection Lewis 2/viewport Lewis clamp true/pause 1000/speak Lewis \"Whoever took part in this appalling act is truly reprehensible. Using my very private item for this sick purpose!$4 / 到底是谁干了这种令人发指的事情，我要强烈谴责！怎么能将我的私人物品用来做这种事情，真是太变态了！$4#$b#And to ruin a perfectly good soup... unforgivable! I've never been more ashamed of this community... Truly disgusting.$4 / 还毁掉了一锅完美的汤……不可饶恕！我从未觉得这个社区如此令我蒙羞……真的很恶心。$4\"/pause 500/faceDirection Lewis 0/emote Lewis 12/speak Lewis \"Go home, the festival is over.$s / 回家吧，节日结束了。$s\"/pause 500/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/message \"I guess the 'little prank' didn't go over too well... / 我猜这个“小恶作剧”并不是很成功……\"/pause 500/message \"Time to head home. / 该回家了。\"/waitForOtherPlayers festivalEnd/end",
        "governorReaction5": "emote Governor 40/pause 400/speak Governor \"Hmmm... Well it's not bad, but it's missing something...$s / 唔……嗯……味道不错，不过，好像缺了点什么……$s#$b#Did everyone in town contribute an ingredient to the soup? I feel like it's missing someone's unique voice. / 镇上的所有人都给汤添加过材料了吗？我感觉好像少了一个人的独特味道。\"/showFrame Governor 0/pause 400/showFrame Lewis 18/emote Lewis 28/pause 600/showFrame Lewis 0/pause 400/move Lewis 2 0 2/move Lewis 0 2 3/pause 500/animate Lewis false false 200 19 19 22 23 23 22 23 23 22 19 19/pause 800/playSound gulp/pause 600/playSound gulp/pause 1000/speak Lewis \"You're right... It's a little bland.$s / 您说的没错……汤有点淡。$s\"/pause 1000/speak Lewis \"Well, thanks for joining us this year, Governor. Sorry the soup wasn't anything special. / 感谢您的参加，州长先生。这汤做得有点普通，实在很抱歉。\"/pause 500/faceDirection Lewis 2/speak Lewis \"Now... who else wants some soup? / 那么……还有人想喝点儿汤吗？\"/faceDirection Marnie 0 true/moveToSoup/pause 1000/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 300/message \"The soup was bland, but the luau was still fun! / 汤是淡了点，不过宴会还是挺有意思的！\"/pause 500/message \"Time to head home. / 该回家了。\"/waitForOtherPlayers festivalEnd/end",
        "governorReaction4": "emote Governor 16/pause 600/shake Governor 1000/jump Governor/pause 800/playMusic SettlingIn/speak Governor \"Oh my... that's the best soup I've ever tasted!$h / 噢……我从没喝过这么好喝的汤！$h\"/shake Governor 5000/animate Governor false true 100 9 10 11 11 10/pause 800/move Lewis 2 0 2/move Lewis 0 2 3/pause 500/animate Lewis false false 200 19 19 22 23 23 22 23 23 22 19 19/pause 800/playSound gulp/pause 600/playSound gulp/pause 1000/speak Lewis \"You're right... It's delicious!$h / 您说得没错……的确很美味！$h\"/pause 500/faceDirection Lewis 2/speak Lewis \"Wonderful job, everyone! Now... who else wants a taste?$h / 伙计们，表现很棒！那么……还有人想尝尝吗？$h\"/faceDirection Marnie 0 true/moveToSoup/pause 1000/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 300/message \"The Governor wasn't kidding... the soup was out of this world! / 州长先生没有说错……此汤只应天上有！\"/pause 500/message \"Time to head home. / 该回家了。\"/waitForOtherPlayers festivalEnd/end",
        "governorReaction3": "emote Governor 32/pause 400/playMusic jaunty/speak Governor \"Ah... that's a very pleasant soup. The produce from this valley never disappoints! / 啊……这汤真好喝啊。星露谷出品果然必属精品！\"/showFrame Governor 0/pause 400/move Lewis 2 0 2/move Lewis 0 2 3/pause 500/animate Lewis false false 200 19 19 22 23 23 22 23 23 22 19 19/pause 800/playSound gulp/pause 600/playSound gulp/pause 1000/speak Lewis \"Mmm... tasty. You all did very well today. / 嗯……美味。大家今天的表现都很好。\"/pause 500/faceDirection Lewis 2/speak Lewis \"Now... who else wants some soup? / 那么……还有人想喝点儿汤吗？\"/faceDirection Marnie 0 true/moveToSoup/pause 1000/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 300/message \"The Luau was a success! Good thing I brought something tasty for the soup. / 宴会大获成功！还好我给汤底准备了美味的食材。\"/pause 500/message \"Time to head home. / 该回家了。\"/waitForOtherPlayers festivalEnd/end",
        "governorReaction2": "pause 400/playMusic ocean/speak Governor \"Hmm... I don't have much to say about this. It's an average soup. / 唔……嗯……没什么好说的。汤的味道很普通。\"/showFrame Governor 0/pause 400/showFrame Lewis 18/emote Lewis 28/pause 600/showFrame Lewis 0/pause 400/move Lewis 2 0 2/move Lewis 0 2 3/pause 500/animate Lewis false false 200 19 19 22 23 23 22 23 23 22 19 19/pause 800/playSound gulp/pause 600/playSound gulp/pause 1000/speak Lewis \"He's right... It's nothing special. Not bad, though. / 他说得对……味道没什么特别的。虽然也不难喝。\"/pause 500/faceDirection Lewis 2/speak Lewis \"Well... who else wants some soup? / 那么……还有人想喝点儿汤吗？\"/faceDirection Marnie 0 true/moveToSoup/pause 1000/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 300/message \"The soup was just average, but otherwise the Luau was a success! / 汤的味道很普通。不过宴会很成功！\"/pause 500/message \"Time to head home. / 该回家了。\"/waitForOtherPlayers festivalEnd/end",
        "governorReaction1": "emote Governor 28/pause 400/playMusic ocean/speak Governor \"Um... It's actually kind of disgusting. I think I'll pass on the soup this year.$s / 呃……好恶心的味道啊。接下来一整年都不想喝汤了。$s\"/showFrame Governor 0/pause 400/showFrame Lewis 18/emote Lewis 28/pause 600/showFrame Lewis 0/pause 400/move Lewis 2 0 2/move Lewis 0 2 3/pause 500/animate Lewis false false 200 19 19 22 23 23 22 23 23 22 19 19/pause 800/playSound gulp/pause 600/playSound gulp/pause 1000/speak Lewis \"Yuck. Someone must have ruined it with a poor-quality ingredient.$s / 呸，一定是有人添加了滥竽充数的食材。$s\"/pause 500/faceDirection Lewis 2/speak Lewis \"Well... does anyone want any? / 那么……还有人想喝汤吗？\"/faceDirection Marnie 0 true/moveToSoup/pause 1000/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 300/message \"The soup wasn't very good, but otherwise the Luau was a success! / 汤不怎么样，不过宴会很成功！\"/pause 500/message \"Time to head home. / 该回家了。\"/waitForOtherPlayers festivalEnd/end",
        "governorReaction0": "pause 500/showFrame Governor 13/pause 500/shake Governor 2000/emote Governor 12/pause 500/speak Governor \"Blech! This is vile! I think I'm going to be sick... $u / 呸！好难喝！我要晕了……$u\"/showFrame Governor 13/jump Lewis/pause 800/speak Governor \"I need to lie down...$u / 得躺下歇一歇……$u\"/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 1000/warp Governor -100 -100/playSound slimedead/faceDirection Lewis 2/viewport 35 12 true/pause 1000/speak Lewis \"Good going, people... Whoever put that foul ingredient in the soup made the Governor pass out! I'm ashamed.$4 / 好样的……到底是谁把脏东西加到汤里的啊，害得州长先生都晕过去了！无耻。$4\"/pause 500/faceDirection Lewis 0/emote Lewis 12/speak Lewis \"Go home, the festival is over.$s / 回家吧，节日到此为止了。$s\"/pause 500/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/message \"What a disaster... / 真是个悲剧……\"/pause 500/message \"Time to head home. / 该回家了。\"/waitForOtherPlayers festivalEnd/end",
        "mainEvent_y2": "pause 500/playMusic ocean/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/loadActors MainEvent/addTemporaryActor Governor 16 32 24 9 2/warpFarmers 24 18 0 28 18 0 32 15 3 26 19 0 20 19 0 15 10 1 15 13 1 34 11 3 right 29 5 2/showFrame Maru 31/showFrame Penny 34/positionOffset Maru 8 24/positionOffset Penny 0 24/positionOffset Jodi 0 16/positionOffset Kent? 8 16/positionOffset Clint 0 -24/positionOffset Haley -8 12/viewport 24 11 true/pause 2000/faceDirection Lewis 3/pause 100/faceDirection Lewis 2/pause 100/faceDirection Lewis 1/pause 100/faceDirection Lewis 2/speak Lewis \"Hello and welcome, everyone! I'm pleased to announce that the potluck ceremony has begun. / 欢迎各位！很高兴能看到大家齐聚在这里。我宣布，百乐汤仪式现在开始。#$b#I have high hopes that you all contributed high-quality ingredients! We want to leave the governor with a good impression, now. / 我希望大家都贡献出了高品质的食材！也希望能够给州长留下最好的印象。\"/pause 1000/faceDirection Lewis 3/pause 500/speak Lewis \"Well... Governor? Would you indulge us with an honorary first tasting? / 州长？能有幸请您首先尝一尝吗？\"/pause 500/speak Governor \"I would be delighted! I've been eyeing the soup all afternoon. / 好的！我盯着那锅汤一下午了。\"/playMusic none/pause 500/move Governor 0 1 2/pause 1000/playSound dwop/showFrame Governor 8 true/pause 1000/animate Governor false false 200 8 8 9 10 11 11/pause 1100/playSound sipTea/pause 1000/playSound gulp/pause 500/showFrame Governor 8 true/animate Governor false false 200 11 10 9 8/pause 900/speak Governor \"...$h / ……$h\"/pause 300/cutscene governorTaste/null",
        "Governor": "What a lovely occasion... It's always a joy to visit Stardew Valley. / 真是美好的时光……星露谷总是那么的赏心悦目。#$e#I must speak to the missus about purchasing a vacation home here. / 回去得跟老婆大人协商下在这里买个度假小屋。",
        "Abigail_spouse": "Don't let me stop you from having fun today. I just feel like watching the sea by myself. / 你不用管我的。我喜欢一个人欣赏海景。",
        "Leah_spouse": "It's nice to see everyone once in a while, but mostly I want to get back to the farm. / 偶尔跟大家聚一聚是好事，但其实我现在只想回去农场里。",
        "Maru_spouse": "Harvey keeps trying to talk to me, but all I want is a piece of this roast. / 哈维一直找我聊天，但我真的只想好好享受这烤肉。",
        "Penny_spouse": "I'm just humoring some old friends. What I really want is a bowl of that soup. / 我正在陪着老朋友谈天说地。但其实我好想尝尝那美味的汤。",
        "Haley_spouse": "Phew... I'm afraid to move, or else I might start to sweat. / 呼……我不敢动，一动就会汗流浃背。",
        "Sebastian_spouse": "I'm doing my best to stay in a good mood... / 我在努力保持着良好的心情……",
        "Sam_spouse": "I guess it wouldn't be very nice to put something nasty in the soup... / 我要是偷偷在汤里加些脏东西不知道会不会太过分嗯……",
        "Alex_spouse": "Hey, I'll take any excuse to come hang out at the beach. This weather is amazing! / 嘿，这么美好的天气，千方百计都要找借口来海边享受下啊！",
        "Harvey_spouse": "Oh dear... I've got sand in my socks...$s / 哎呦……我袜子进沙子了……$s",
        "Elliott_spouse": "The old cabin seems to be holding up well. Every time I return I half expect the thing to be rotted... / 那个陈旧的小屋还真是老当益壮。每次我回去都会有一股屋子破烂到住不下去的心理准备……",
        "Abigail": "It's tiring to socialize with everyone... I'd rather watch the sea. / 与人交际实在太累人……我宁愿一个人静静看海。",
        "Emily": "%She's unresponsive. / %她没有反应。",
        "Robin": "Ow... you stepped on my foot, dear. / 嗷……你踩到我脚的了，亲。",
        "Demetrius": "This is tiring, honey. Are you ready to visit the buffet soon? *pant* / 太累人了，甜心。准备好去吃自助餐没？*喘气*",
        "Maru": "Whatever Linus is roasting smells awfully good... *slurp* / 莱纳斯在烧烤着什么东西？好香啊……*咕噜*",
        "Sebastian": "One year Sam put a pound of anchovies in the potluck soup. / 有一年山姆往百乐汤里加了整整一磅的凤尾鱼。#$e#Ever wondered why Sam leads the town in community service hours?$h / 现在知道为什么山姆的社区服务时数全镇第一了吧？$h",
        "Linus": "A slow, continuous rotation is key to achieving the perfect roast. / 缓慢而均匀的转动是做出完美烧烤的关键。",
        "Pierre": "Hmm... maybe if I get on the governor's good side he'll give my business a tax break... / 嗯……要是我能讨好州长，说不定他会给我减税呢……#$b#I wonder if he likes aged whiskey? / 不知道他喜不喜欢陈年威士忌？#$e#Now if only the Mayor would stop shmoozing with him all afternoon. / 得找机会不让镇长一直跟他闲扯。",
        "Caroline": "I put fresh vegetables from my garden into the communal soup pot. / 我把后院采的新鲜蔬菜加到了汤锅里。",
        "Alex": "Perfect weather for a beach party, huh? / 这么好的天气就该搞个沙滩派对，你说呢？",
        "George": "That music! It's too loud. / 这音乐吵死人了！#$b#Can't I have a little peace and quiet to enjoy the ocean? / 能不能让我静静地观海？",
        "Evelyn": "Ahh... The smell of the ocean takes me back many years. Long before you were born. / 啊……海的味道让我回想起一些陈年往事。那时你还没出生呢。",
        "Lewis": "Look sharp! The governor's here for his annual visit. / 州长要来例行访问了。#$b#If you brought something for the potluck make sure and add it to the soup cauldron. / 你要是带了额外材料来，那就快添加到汤锅里去。",
        "Clint": "I'm full, but what else is there to do besides eat? / 吃得好饱，不过除了吃吃吃也没别的事可以做了。",
        "Penny": "We do this festival every year to give the governor a taste of everything the valley has to offer. / 这个节日我们一年庆祝一次，为的是让州长体验到星露谷的风味。#$e#Mayor Lewis hopes it will get the governor on our good side. That's why he's so neurotic about the way the soup tastes. / 刘易斯镇长希想给州长留下好印象，所以他十分在意汤的味道。",
        "Pam": "Heh... free buffet. One of the perks of living here. Enjoy it, kid! / 嘿嘿……免费大餐。住在星露谷真是福利多多啊。好好享受吧，小子！",
        "Haley": "I would dance, but I don't want to get sweaty. / 我想跳舞，但又怕出汗。",
        "Jodi": "I hope the soup is good this year. / 希望今年的汤味道会不错。",
        "Kent": "Hey, good to see you. / 嘿，很高兴见到你。",
        "Marlon": "I'll be back here by the trees... the air is a lot cooler. / 我要待在树荫这里……这边气候凉爽多了。",
        "Sam": "Governor? Who cares... / 州长？管他呢……#$e#Why should I care about some random old guy? / 我干嘛要在意不认识的老家伙？",
        "Leah": "How's the farming coming along? It must be a busy season for you. / 农活怎么样了？这一季忙坏了吧。",
        "Shane": "Wow... you don't get hot pepper chutney like this in the big city... / 哇……大城市里面可买不到这种辣椒酱……",
        "Marnie": "If you brought something for the soup, climb the stairs on the other side and throw it in. / 你要是带来了煮汤的材料，那就爬上那边的梯子把汤料丢进锅里。",
        "Elliott": "I woke up late, stepped out of the door and found myself in the middle of all this hubbub! / 我起晚了，一出门就发现已经身处喧闹之中！#$e#I forgot that today was the Luau.$h / 我都忘了今天是宴会日。$h",
        "Gus": "These blasted sand-flies keep landing on the food! / 该死的沙蝇一直停靠在食物上！",
        "Dwarf": "You say it's raining up above? *gasp* / 地面上下雨了？*喘气*#$e#Rain... It's almost mythical to us. Some of us live our entire lives without ever experiencing it. / 下雨……这是个很陌生的概念。我们大部分人一辈子都没经历过下雨。",
        "Wizard": "The merpeople are curious about your festivities. / 鱼群们对你们的节日很感兴趣。#$e#They become upset when you litter into the ocean. / 但它们不喜欢你们把垃圾往海里扔。",
        "Harvey": "Good thing I came with sunscreen. / 还好我带了防晒霜。#$e#I wonder if Maru could use some sunscreen on her shoulders? / 不知道玛鲁需不需要？",
        "Sandy": "I heard it's raining back home. Is that why you came here?$h / 听说家乡在下雨。你是为避雨才跑来这里的吗？$h#$e#I kind of miss the rain, actually...$s / 话说我有点怀念雨景了……$s",
        "Jas": "Vincent isn't a good dancer. / 文森特舞跳得不怎么样。",
        "Vincent": "I'm bored... / 好无聊……",
        "Willy": "Hi there, @. Taking a breather? / 你好啊，@！在忙里偷闲吗？#$e#To tell you the truth, I'd rather be fishing right now. / 讲真，这里好无聊哦，我宁愿去钓鱼。",
        "Leo": "Shhh... I'm learning the secrets of the perfect roast. / 嘘……我在学习完美烤肉的秘诀。",
        "Governor_y2": "I eagerly anticipate my visit to Stardew Valley each year. There's a palpable charm in the air! / 我每年去星露谷都很期待，这里到处都能感受到无比的魅力！",
        "Abigail_spouse_y2": "After the soup tasting, let's go hang out on the docks away from everyone.$0 / 喝完汤之后，我们去码头上逛逛吧，那里没什么人。$0",
        "Penny_spouse_y2": "I heard a rumor that the governor is considering buying a vacation home here.$0 / 我听说州长正在考虑在这里买一套度假别墅。$0",
        "Leah_spouse_y2": "You better grab a plate before it's all gone!$1 / 赶紧拿一点，不然都被吃光了！$1",
        "Haley_spouse_y2": "I'm tempted to run back home and grab my bikini.$0 / 我真想跑回家去换上比基尼。$0#$b#The water's at a perfect temperature... I dipped my little toe in!$1 / 现在水温正正好好……我用小脚趾试过了！$1",
        "Maru_spouse_y2": "It's cooler back here in the shade. I'll join you at the buffet soon, okay?$0 / 这里比较阴凉，我过会儿再去餐桌那里找你，好吗？$0",
        "Emily_spouse_y2": "*pant* It might be time to take a break soon.$0 / （喘气）差不多该休息一下了。$0#$e#We should dance together later, okay?$1 / 我们过会儿再一起跳舞，好吗？$1",
        "Harvey_spouse_y2": "This music is making my legs move on their own... just like aerobics class!$0 / 听着音乐，我的双腿自己就动起来了……仿佛在上有氧健身课！$0",
        "Alex_spouse_y2": "Today... I eat as much as I want. I'll do extra push-ups tomorrow!$0 / 今天……我要大吃特吃，大不了明天多做几个俯卧撑！$0",
        "Sam_spouse_y2": "That soup is smelling zesty... / 汤的味道好香……#$e#Did you add something good? I'm getting hungry!$1 / 你加了什么好吃的东西吗？我好馋！$1",
        "Sebastian_spouse_y2": "Do you remember when you caught me in this spot on that rainy day?$0 / 你还记得那天下雨，我站在这里被你发现了吗？$0#$e#Even though this is my solo spot... I was really glad you came.$1 / 这里是我独处的地方……但我真的很庆幸你过来了。$1",
        "Elliott_spouse_y2": "I would suggest we make time for a little 'rendezvous' in my old cabin... but I'm afraid it's become rather... musty... in my absence. / 我们要不要到我的小屋里悄悄约个会……不过我担心我离开之后那里可能……有点发霉……",
        "Shane_spouse_y2": "Mmm... that roast smells good.$0 / 嗯……烤肉闻起来真香。$0",
        "Abigail_y2": "My dad's obsessed with the governor's visit. Everything has to be perfect! / 州长来访，我爸心神不宁的，非得要把一切都做到完美！#$e#I think he's hoping to be mayor some day...$9 / 我估计他想有朝一日当上镇长……$9",
        "Robin_y2": "Demetrius... It's because it's fun!%noturn$5 / 德米特里厄斯……那是因为开心啊！%noturn$5",
        "Demetrius_y2": "Why do humans enjoy dancing? Perhaps it is an instinctual mechanism, so that we will inadvertently convey our genetic quality to potential mates?%noturn / 人类为什么喜欢跳舞呢？也许是一种本能机制，方便我们不经意间将基因好坏传达给选择的配偶？%noturn",
        "Maru_y2": "Ow... this bench has been cooking in the sun all day.$2 / 哎哟……这椅子怕是在烈日下晒了一整天吧。$2",
        "Sebastian_y2": "Oh, hey. Looking to escape the noise too?$0 / 啊，你好。你也想要远离吵闹的地方吗？$0",
        "Linus_y2": "Ah, can you smell that?$0 / 啊，你闻到了吗？$0#$b#It's a signal that the roast is almost ready!$1 / 这就代表肉马上要烤好了！$1",
        "Pierre_y2": "The moment Lewis steps away from the governor... that's my moment to rub elbows...$0 / 等刘易斯从州长身边离开……我就凑上去打招呼……$0#$e#Ah, I didn't see you there.$4 / 啊，你怎么在这里。$4#$e#If you want to buy something, talk to me on the other side of the counter.$1 / 你如果想买东西的话，到柜台对面跟我说吧。$1",
        "Caroline_y2": "Gus used my potatoes to make several dishes for the buffet.$0 / 格斯用我家的土豆给自助餐做了好几道菜。$0#$e#So, what kind of ingredient are you adding to the soup?$0 / 怎么说，你打算往汤里面加什么食材？$0",
        "Alex_y2": "Do you think if I went in the water, other people would follow? I don't want to be a solo swimmer!$0 / 如果我下水，你觉得其他人会一起来吗？我可不想一个人游泳！$0",
        "George_y2": "Leek and garlic mashed potatoes? Hehe... honey, I think I've died and gone to heaven!%noturn$1 / 有韭葱大蒜土豆泥？嘿嘿……亲爱的，这里是不是天堂啊！%noturn$1",
        "Evelyn_y2": "Now, don't overeat dear. I wouldn't want you getting a stomach ache.%noturn$0 / 好了，亲爱的，别吃太多，我可不想让你再犯胃痛。%noturn$0",
        "Lewis_y2": "The governor is our distinguished guest today! I expect all of you to be on your best behavior. / 州长是我们今天的贵宾！希望大家都能好好表现。#$b#For those who brought something for the potluck, contribute your ingredients to the soup cauldron. / 给百乐汤带了食材的人，把东西放进汤锅里就行。",
        "Clint_y2": "*munch* This festival always has the best food. / （咀嚼）这个节日的美食是最好吃的。",
        "Penny_y2": "Isn't it wonderful to see our community come together like this? I try my best to treasure these moments.$0 / 大伙齐聚在这里，多开心呀！我会用心记住这样的时刻。$0",
        "Pam_y2": "*slurp* Oh, yeah! I'm gonna need more of this!$1 / （咕嘟咕嘟）太棒啦！这个我要多来一点！$1",
        "Emily_y2": "*pant* It's all in the hips!$0 / （喘气）屁股要扭起来！$0#$e#I think I need to take a break soon. I'm getting sweaty!$0 / 我得歇一会儿了，出了好多汗！$0",
        "Haley_y2": "Don't block the sun! I'm in just the right spot to avoid getting any tan lines.$0 / 不要挡着阳光！我这个位置刚好不会弄出晒痕。$0",
        "Jodi_y2": "I've heard the summer season gets very busy for farmers. Make sure you don't overwork yourself!$0 / 听说夏季的农活很多，千万不要劳累过度了啊！$0",
        "Kent_y2": "*sniff* ...smells are powerful for bringing back memories...$0 / （闻了一下）……气味总能唤起以前的记忆……$0#$e#That can be good or bad... / 有好也有坏……",
        "Marlon_y2": "Hello. / 你好。#$e#Soup? Dancing? No thank you. I'm perfectly content right here. Besides, someone needs to keep watch in case a monster appears...$0 / 汤？跳舞？不用了，我待在这里就足够了，而且总得有人看着，万一冒出来什么怪物……$0",
        "Sam_y2": "Next year, I gotta remember to bring my electric guitar... Imagine a solo at this part of the song!$0 / 明年我一定要记得带上电吉他……这首歌的这一段来一段独奏，那可太妙了！$0",
        "Leah_y2": "I can't seem to decide what to eat! There's too many options to choose from.$0 / 我到底要吃哪个啊！看得我眼花缭乱。$0",
        "Shane_y2": "I'll never turn down free food. / 白吃白喝我肯定不会拒绝。",
        "Marnie_y2": "Hello, @! Did you bring an ingredient for the potluck? Just climb the stairs and toss it right in!$1 / @，你好！你带了食材吗？爬上梯子丢进百乐汤里就行了！$1",
        "Elliott_y2": "Ah, the Luau... all the hustle and bustle of town brought to my very doorstep!$0 / 啊，夏威夷宴会……一开门就能见到平时小镇里的熙熙攘攘！$0",
        "Gus_y2": "One bad ingredient can ruin the whole soup...$0 / 一个糟糕的食材，就会坏了一锅汤……$0",
        "Wizard_y2": "In the dark depths of the sea lie many mysteries, waiting to be uncovered.$0 / 大海深处蕴藏着太多秘密，等待着被人发现。$0",
        "Harvey_y2": "*pant*... *pant*... ahhhh, I can't wait for a bowl of piping hot soup...$h / （不停喘气）……啊啊啊，快给我喝一碗热气腾腾的汤吧……$h",
        "Jas_y2": "B...But... Do I have to eat it?$2 / 我……我必须得吃吗？$2",
        "Vincent_y2": "Why can't I go play by the tide pools?$s / 为什么我不能去水洼那边玩？$s",
        "Willy_y2": "Don't worry, I'll be back for the soup... I'm just enjoying a tender moment with me pipe!$3 / 别担心，我会回来喝汤的……我就去抽个烟！$3",
        "Leo_y2": "My home is that way, across the ocean. It feels so close, but so far away.$0 / 我的老家就在那个方向，在大海的那头，感觉很近，却又非常遥远。$0#$e#I hope my friends are doing well.$0 / 希望朋友们过得还好。$0"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Festivals/summer28",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "name": "Dance Of The Moonlight Jellies / 月光水母之舞",
        "mainEvent": "pause 500/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/loadActors MainEvent/changeLocation Beach/warpFarmers 28 36 2 29 35 2 34 36 2 37 35 2 25 36 2 10 39 3 30 35 2 33 35 2 36 35 2 up 25 33 3/positionOffset farmer 0 16/warp spouse 29 36/faceDirection spouse 2/specificTemporarySprite candleBoat/showFrame Pam 24/positionOffset Pam 0 12/showFrame Haley 30/viewport 26 36 true/pause 2000/move Lewis 0 1 2/move Lewis -2 0 3/pause 400/showFrame Lewis 16 true/animate Lewis false false 200 25 16 17 17/pause 800/playSound parry/specificTemporarySprite candleBoatMove/pause 500/showFrame Lewis 0 true/animate Lewis false false 200 25 12/pause 400/move Lewis 1 0 2/pause 6000/specificTemporarySprite moonlightJellies/pause 10000/playMusic moonlightJellies/pause 18000/emote Jodi 16 true/pause 800/emote Emily 16 true/pause 700/emote Abigail 56 true/pause 8500/move Jas 0 1 2/pause 300/faceDirection Jas 3 true/pause 300/jump Jas 8 true/pause 500/emote Jas 20/pause 500/viewport move -1 0 8000/pause 4000/move Caroline -2 0 3 true/pause 4000/faceDirection Sebastian 2/move Abigail 1 0 2/showFrame Abigail 24/pause 500/viewport move 1 0 21000/pause 5000/move Lewis 0 1 2/showFrame Lewis 18/pause 3000/showFrame Haley 31/pause 100/showFrame Haley 24/pause 1000/showFrame Haley 31/pause 100/showFrame Haley 30/pause 1800/showFrame Jodi 25/pause 1000/showFrame Emily 27/showFrame Haley 31/pause 100/showFrame Haley 24/pause 1000/showFrame Haley 31/pause 100/showFrame Haley 30/pause 1000/move Clint -1 0 2/pause 2000/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 2000/pause 1000/message \"The glow of summer has faded, now... and the moonlight jellies carry on toward the great unknown. / 夏日的光芒渐渐消失……而月光水母继续向着神秘的未知世界前行。\"/playMusic none/pause 2000/waitForOtherPlayers festivalEnd/end",
        "Leah_spouse": "Hey. I'm paying my respects to another bygone summer. I'll come meet up with you when we launch the candle-boat. / 啊，我在致敬又一个离我们远去的夏季。等开始放烛灯船时我会来找你的。",
        "Abigail": "Such a rare and exciting thing...  / 想想都让人有点小激动……",
        "Robin": "*yawn*... It's past my bed-time.$s / *哈欠*……一不留神都过了我一般的就寝时间。$s#$e#Hey, did you see that candle-boat? I crafted it myself.$h / 嘿，看见那艘烛灯船了吗？那是我亲手做的。$h",
        "Demetrius": "The 'Moonlight Jelly'... what a remarkable species! We're very lucky that they stop here on their long journey south. / “月光水母”……多么奇特的生物啊！它们在南迁的漫长旅途中会停歇于此，真是我们的福气。#$e#It's unknown why they are attracted to light... very curious. / 不过还是很好奇它们为什么会趋光而行。",
        "Maru": "It's kind of cold, actually. I guess fall is right around the corner. / 天气有点冷了。秋天快要来临了。",
        "Sebastian": "I thought I saw something moving in there... something big, something dark. / 我好像看到那边有些东西……庞大而黑暗的怪物。#$e#Just trying to scare you...$h / 哈哈，吓唬你而已……$h",
        "Pierre": "Psst... Make sure to swing by the shop tomorrow to get your fall seeds! / 喂……记得明天到店里来拿你的秋季种子！",
        "Caroline": "These candles are romantic, aren't they? / 好多好多蜡烛，好浪漫啊！你觉得呢？",
        "Linus": "I'll just sneak up when the jellies arrive... I don't want to bother anyone. / 等水母抵达后我就潜行过去……我不想惊动任何人。",
        "Alex": "I can't believe summer's over... I feel like it just started.$s / 难以置信夏天就这么结束了……宛如昨天才刚开始。$s",
        "George": "What, why are you looking at me like that? You think I'm too old to enjoy something like this? / 你干嘛这样看着我？是不是觉得我一把年纪了就不适合这种场合？",
        "Evelyn": "I remember seeing the jellies once, as a little girl. Oh, how I jumped with joy when they arrived! / 我小时候曾经见过水母。嗷，那时候看见水母抵达我那叫一个兴奋啊！#$e#But that was long ago... I'm a lot less energetic now. / 不过都是很久以前的事了……我现在已经没有那么精力充沛了。",
        "Lewis": "Good evening, @. The Moonlight Jellies are close... I already saw one glowing in the distance. / 晚上好，@。月光水母快来临了……我已经看到了远方传来的微光。#$b#Once we launch the candle-boat they'll come up to the docks and say hello. / 等我们把烛灯船放出去，它们就会被吸引过来跟我们打招呼。",
        "Clint": "I wore my special shoes tonight... No one noticed.$s / 我今晚穿上了最美丽的鞋子……但却没人欣赏。$s",
        "Emily": "Look out there, at the endless sea. Deep underwater, all kinds of life forms are moving around in the dark. / 你看那漫漫海洋的水底下，各种各样的生物在黑暗中游走。#$b#Eerie, isn't it? / 是不是好恐怖的样子？",
        "Penny": "Life is so easy for a jellyfish... just letting the waves carry you onward forever. / 水母的生活过得真轻松……随波逐流，一生全靠浪。",
        "Pam": "Don't tell Gus, but I'm a little disappointed there's no buffet tonight. / 今晚没有大餐我好失望啊，不过你别告诉格斯。",
        "Haley": "I'm gonna take a picture of the jellies when they arrive. / 真该带上相机的！我老是不记得。",
        "Jodi": "There! I just saw something glowing! / 那里！有东西在发光！#$b#Oh... It's gone.$s / 唉！一眨眼就消失了。$s",
        "Kent": "Good evening, @. Hope you can find some time to relax before the harvest season. / 晚上好，@。希望你能在收获季节前找点时间放松一下。",
        "Sam": "I wonder if they're poisonous? / 不知道它们有没有毒？#$e#Maybe I shouldn't push Sebastian in the water after all...$h / 有点后悔把塞巴斯蒂安推进水里了……$h",
        "Leah": "Hey. I'm paying my respects to another bygone summer.  / 啊，我在致敬又一个离我们远去的夏季。",
        "Shane": "The jellies were here a year ago, and they'll be back again a year from now... nature is amazing. / 水母一年前来过这里，一年后今天又来了，明年今日还会再来……大自然真是奇妙。",
        "Marnie": "That's a heavy load of people for an ancient wooden dock! I'll stay over here near the beach. / 这么陈旧的木制码头却挤满了人！我还是待在沙滩上吧。",
        "Elliott": "If we keep polluting the oceans, the jellies will surely go extinct. It's already in the process of happening. / 我们继续污染海水的话，水母肯定会灭绝的。这事已经有征兆了。#$e#What a shame... we have no respect for nature anymore. / 可惜啊……人们都不再畏惧大自然了。",
        "Gus": "'Moonlight Jellies'... I wonder how they taste?$h / “月光水母”……不知道尝起来味道如何？$h#$b#I would never try it, of course!$u / 不过，我当然不会对它们下毒手的，嗯嗯，一定不会！$u",
        "Dwarf": "You say it's raining up above? *gasp* / 地面上下雨了？*喘气*#$e#Rain... It's almost mythical to us. Some of us live our entire lives without ever experiencing it. / 下雨……这是个很陌生的概念。我们大部分人一辈子都没经历过下雨。",
        "Wizard": "How did you find me back here? I thought I was well-hidden. / 你是怎么找到我的？我还以为躲藏得很隐秘呢。#$b#Perhaps you are blessed with the gift of clairvoyance. / 也许是你的洞察力超凡入圣。#$e#I'm here to observe the Lunaloos... or 'Moonlight Jellies', as you call them. They possess an unusually potent magical aura for an aquatic life form. / 其实我是来看露娜洛尔的……也就是你们所谓的月光水母。它们的生命形式让我很好奇。",
        "Harvey": "Well, summer's over. To be honest, I'll be happy to say goodbye to these blasted mosquitos! / 嗯，夏天结束了。其实我很高兴，终于能摆脱那烦人的蚊子了！",
        "Sandy": "I heard it's raining back home. Is that why you came here?$h / 听说家乡在下雨。你是为避雨才跑来这里的吗？$h#$e#I kind of miss the rain, actually...$s / 话说我有点怀念雨景了……$s",
        "Jas": "I hope there are babies this year! / 希望今年会有宝宝诞生！",
        "Vincent": "I wanna see the rare green jelly! / 好想看罕见的绿色水母！",
        "Willy": "Most night-fish would be scared of the light... these are strange ones. / 大部分夜间水生生物都畏光……这些水母真奇特。",
        "Leo": "The moonlight jellies are my old friends... they come to the island every year, too. / 月光水母是我的老朋友了……它们每年也都会来到岛上。",
        "mainEvent_y2": "pause 500/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/loadActors MainEvent/changeLocation Beach/warpFarmers 28 36 2 26 36 2 33 35 2 40 35 2 27 35 2 30 35 2 37 34 2 39 34 2 up 42 35 3/positionOffset farmer 0 16/warp spouse 29 36/faceDirection spouse 2/warp Caroline 36 35/faceDirection Caroline 2 true/warp Pierre 37 35/faceDirection Pierre 2 true/specificTemporarySprite candleBoat/viewport 26 36 true/pause 2000/move Lewis 0 1 2/move Lewis -2 0 3/pause 400/showFrame Lewis 16 true/animate Lewis false false 200 25 16 17 17/pause 800/playSound parry/specificTemporarySprite candleBoatMove/pause 500/showFrame Lewis 0 true/animate Lewis false false 200 25 12/pause 400/faceDirection Lewis 2/pause 6000/specificTemporarySprite moonlightJellies/pause 10000/playMusic moonlightJellies/pause 18000/emote Robin 16/pause 500/emote Jodi 56/pause 500/jump Maru/pause 500/emote Penny 20/pause 1250/emote Caroline 16/pause 1250/faceDirection Robin 1 true/pause 750/faceDirection Demetrius 3 true/pause 2000/faceDirection Robin 2 true/pause 750/faceDirection Demetrius 2 true/pause 2500/showFrame Willy 24/pause 500/showFrame Willy 25/pause 1500/viewport move -1 0 8000/pause 2650/showFrame Kent 16/pause 1500/move Jodi 0 1 2/pause 1500/showFrame Jodi 25/pause 4500/faceDirection Vincent 2 true/pause 300/faceDirection Vincent 1 true/pause 150/move Vincent 1 0 2/move Vincent 0 2 2/pause 600/jump Vincent/pause 400/viewport move 1 0 20000/pause 2000/faceDirection Vincent 1 true/pause 1000/faceDirection Vincent 2 true/pause 1000/move Lewis 1 0 2/move Lewis 0 1 2/showFrame Lewis 18/pause 4300/showFrame Demetrius 19/pause 3000/faceDirection Caroline 1 true/pause 1000/faceDirection Pierre 3 true/pause 2000/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 2000/pause 1000/message \"The glow of summer has faded, now... and the moonlight jellies carry on toward the great unknown. / 夏日的光芒渐渐消失……而月光水母继续向着神秘的未知世界前行。\"/playMusic none/pause 2000/waitForOtherPlayers festivalEnd/end",
        "Abigail_spouse_y2": "I brought a blanket for us in case we get cold later.$0 / 我带了毯子，万一过会儿天凉了咱们可以裹上。$0#$e#It's a little small, but I'm sure we can make it work...$4 / 毯子有点小，不过应该可以凑合用……$4",
        "Haley_spouse_y2": "Aww... It's so romantic, with all the candles.$4 / 哇……有这么多蜡烛，太浪漫了。$4#$e#Goodbye, Summer...$s / 再见了，夏天……$s",
        "Maru_spouse_y2": "Do you think I have enough time to grab my telescope from the farmhouse?$0 / 你觉得我还来得及回农场拿望远镜吗？$0#$e#Hmm... probably not. I don't want to miss this!$0 / 唔……估计来不及了。可不能错过这个！$0",
        "Emily_spouse_y2": "Hey, there you are!$0 / 哎，你在这里啊！$0#$e#The ocean holds so many secrets and wonders. It's truly amazing.$0 / 海洋蕴藏着这么多秘密和奇观，太神奇了。$0",
        "Leah_spouse_y2": "I brought some sparkling wine for the main event... Summer's not over yet!$0 / 我带了点起泡酒，过会儿可以喝……夏天还没结束呢！$0",
        "Penny_spouse_y2": "I would've brought us a pot of tea if I had known it would be this chilly!$0 / 早知道这么冷，我就带一壶茶来了！$0",
        "Alex_spouse_y2": "I'm just spending some time with the family for a moment. I'll meet you on the docks soon, okay?$0 / 我先和家里人待一会儿，过会儿在码头见，好吗？$0",
        "Sam_spouse_y2": "Wow... you look great tonight!$10 / 哇……你现在真好看！$10",
        "Harvey_spouse_y2": "Hi, honey. It'll be any moment now when the jellies show up... It never gets old!$0 / 哎，亲爱的，水母随时都可能出现……根本看不厌！$0",
        "Shane_spouse_y2": "Are you all prepared for the fall? I am... / 你为秋天做好准备了吗？我准备好了……#$e#Huh? Oh, I bought a king size bag of pumpkin chips. You can have one, if you want. / 嗯？哦，这是我买的超大袋南瓜片，你可以尝尝。",
        "Sebastian_spouse_y2": "I remember the first Moonlight Jellies festival that you came to. / 我还记得你第一次来月光水母节的时候。#$b#You didn't notice, but I was watching you when the jellies came up. You looked beautiful in that blue light...$l / 你可能没注意到，水母出现的时候其实我在看着你。蓝色光映照着，你真的很好看……$l",
        "Elliott_spouse_y2": "Ah, I was wondering when you would arrive!$0 / 啊，我还在想你什么时候来呢！$0#$e#Let's head to the docks soon, and welcome our aquatic guests!$1 / 咱们赶紧去码头吧，水母快要来了！$1",
        "Abigail_y2": "Apparently there's a rare green jelly. I want to be the first to see it tonight!$0 / 据说有一种稀有的绿色水母，今晚我一定要第一个看到！$0",
        "Robin_y2": "Every year, I make sure to inspect the candle-boat, and patch any holes. / 每年我都会检查一遍烛灯船，把破损的地方修补好。#$e#Imagine if it sank during the festival...$1 / 万一节日的时候沉了可就不好了……$1",
        "Demetrius_y2": "There's a different kind of 'jelly', that anglers sometimes pull out of the water. Despite the name, they are very different in nature to the Moonlight Jellies... / 钓鱼的时候有可能钓到一种“凝胶”，虽然不是活物，但你还别说，质感跟月光水母有点像呢……",
        "Maru_y2": "Do you see a faint glow on the horizon? That must be them!$0 / 你看到海平面上的微光了吗？肯定是它们来了！$0",
        "Sebastian_y2": "When you stare into the ocean, there's a chance something down there is looking back at you...$0 / 当你凝视大海的时候，大海里可能有东西也在凝视着你……$0",
        "Linus_y2": "I noticed no one else was using this dock, so I quietly snuck down.$0 / 我看到没有人在用码头，就悄悄溜过来了。$0#$e#I like watching the jellies, too. / 我也很喜欢看水母。",
        "Pierre_y2": "Hello, farmer @. Be sure to drop by my store tomorrow to purchase your fall seeds!$0 / 你好啊，农夫@。明天记得来我的商店买秋季种子啊！$0",
        "Caroline_y2": "I'm happy the jellies choose to visit us during their trip south. It's a magical moment our community can share together.$0 / 我很庆幸水母南下的路上会路过这里，我们大伙可以共同见证这一梦幻的时刻。$0",
        "Alex_y2": "It's a shame that summer has to be over, but I guess that's life...$0 / 夏天就这么过去了真可惜，可能这就是生活吧……$0",
        "George_y2": "Back in the old days, we used to scoop 'em up and put 'em in jars...$h / 以前我们会把它们捞起来，放进罐子里……$h#$e#Times have changed... Times have changed... / 都已经过去这么多年了啊……",
        "Evelyn_y2": "George and I have been watching the jellies come and go together for decades now.$1 / 我和乔治看水母来来去去已经有几十年了。$1",
        "Lewis_y2": "Greetings, @. As the evening sets in, the Moonlight Jellies draw closer to the shoreline. / @，晚上好。趁着夜幕降临，月光水母会逐渐靠近海岸。#$b#Once we set the candle-boat on its way, they'll gather around the docks.$0 / 我们把烛灯船放出去之后，它们就会聚集到码头周围。$0",
        "Clint_y2": "I got too close to a wave, and it soaked my foot...$2 / 我离海浪太近了，脚被弄湿了……$2",
        "Penny_y2": "Brr... that's a chilly breeze. I should've worn a hat! / 嘶……这风好冷，我应该戴个帽子的！",
        "Pam_y2": "Hey, kid. You're a farmer. So tell me... can you make jelly out of these things? / 哎，孩子，你经营着农场吧，我问你……用这些玩意儿能做果酱吗？#$e#Would save me a lot of money if I could top my toast that way!$1 / 可以的话，我用来涂面包就能省不少钱！$1",
        "Emily_y2": "The moonlight jellies possess a deep blue aura of mystery...$0 / 月光水母散发出神秘的深蓝色光芒……$0#$e#There's more to them than meets the eye.$0 / 它们肯定不像看上去那么简单。$0",
        "Haley_y2": "I didn't have time to put on makeup... Do you think anyone would notice in the dark? / 我没来得及化妆……天色这么暗，应该没人注意到吧？",
        "Jodi_y2": "The full moon will guide the jellies to our shore. / 满月会指引水母来到这片海岸。",
        "Kent_y2": "Hey. Got big plans for the fall? / 哎，秋季有什么计划吗？",
        "Marlon_y2": "I may only have one good eye left, but I assure you I will spot any fell creature lurking in the dark. / 虽然我只有一只眼睛看得清，但是我跟你保证，那些暗中潜伏的猛兽我一个都不会漏看。",
        "Sam_y2": "Summer is drawing to a close. I'm gonna miss the long days! / 夏天要结束了，要是白天一直这么长就好了！",
        "Leah_y2": "Have any fun plans for the fall season? I need to decorate my house soon. / 秋天有什么有趣的计划吗？我准备装饰一下我的房子。",
        "Shane_y2": "I wonder how many will show up this year?$0 / 今年会出现多少只呢？$0",
        "Marnie_y2": "I can't go any further on the dock. The sounds of creaking wood is causing me to tremble.$s / 我没法走到码头前面了，听到木头嘎吱的声音我就发抖。$s#$e#When I was a little girl, I fell through a rotten dock once, and it traumatized me...$s / 我小时候有一次在码头踩到腐烂的木头落水了，然后就有了心理阴影……$s",
        "Elliott_y2": "The candle lights shimmering on the water are simply breathtaking. It looks like a painting coming to life.$0 / 烛光在水上摇曳，真是美得像油画一般。$0",
        "Gus_y2": "*sniff* Ahh... the fresh smell of the ocean never fails to satisfy.$0 / （深吸一口气）啊……大海的味道总能令人满足。$0",
        "Wizard_y2": "The glowing eggs of the Lunaloos make for a potent reagent... / 露娜洛尔的发光卵可以做成强力的试剂。",
        "Harvey_y2": "With each passing second, my anticipation grows...$0 / 每过一秒，我的期待就增加一分。$0",
        "Sandy_y2": "I heard it's raining back home. Is that why you came here?$h / I heard it's raining back home. Is that why coo came here?$h#$e#I kind of miss the rain, actually...$s / I kind of miss the rain, actually...$s",
        "Jas_y2": "How do the jellies know where to swim if they don't have eyes?$0 / 水母没有眼睛，是怎么知道往哪里游的？$0",
        "Vincent_y2": "I touched a jelly once and it stung my hand.$2 / 我摸过一次水母，结果手被蜇了。$2",
        "Willy_y2": "It's an old fisherman's rule... if you ever fish up a moonlight jelly, you gotta throw her back into the sea.$0 / 渔夫有一条老规矩……如果钓到月光水母，就必须扔回海里。$0",
        "Leo_y2": "My old friends from home are visiting us soon!$1 / 我的老朋友们很快就要来看我们了！$1"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Festivals/fall16",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "name": "Stardew Valley Fair / 星露谷展览会",
        "Abigail_spouse": "I beat all these games last year!$h / 去年我打通了这些游戏！$h",
        "Leah_spouse": "I learned all of Robin's techniques last year, but she's always one step ahead of me! / 去年我学会了罗宾的所有技巧，但她总是领先我一步！",
        "Maru_spouse": "mumph... This is my one chance to pig out on barbecue sandwiches. / 嗯……有机会在三明治烤肉派对上大吃特吃了。",
        "Penny_spouse": "I hope we win the grange display contest! / 希望我们能赢得农庄展览大赛！",
        "Haley_spouse": "Did you remember to bring good stuff for our grange display? I hope we win this year. / 你记得为我们的农庄展览带来好东西吗？我希望我们今年能赢。",
        "Sebastian_spouse": "Hey, @. I'm just catching up with Sam. Go ahead and have some fun. / 嘿，@。我正好碰上了山姆。去尽情玩耍吧。",
        "Sam_spouse": "Sebastian's the same as always. Are you having fun at the festival? / 塞巴斯蒂安还是老样子。你在节日里玩得开心吗？",
        "Alex_spouse": "I'm just catching up with some old friends... you go on and have a good time. / 我正好碰上了一些老朋友……你继续玩得开心。",
        "Harvey_spouse": "I'll wait here until you're ready to go home... / 你准备好回家时我会在这里等你……",
        "Elliott_spouse": "The smokey aroma drew me here, yet 'twas the zesty sauce that truly sealed my fate... *gurgle*$s / 烟熏香气吸引我来这，但真正留我在这的是辣酱……*咯咯声*$s",
        "Abigail": "I already beat all the games... now what? / 我已经通关了所有游戏。现在干啥？",
        "Robin": "Woodworking is an ancient tradition that I'm very proud to be a part of.$h / 木工活是一项传统工艺，我很自豪能参与其中。$h",
        "Demetrius": "Robin really works hard on her carpentry stuff... she deserves a little recognition now and then. / 罗宾做木工活儿做得很用心……她值得被人们认可。",
        "Maru": "*slurp* mmm... this barbecue sauce is amazing.$h / *咕噜* 太美味了。这烤肉酱太好吃了。$h",
        "Sebastian": "It's kinda hectic today... I'm just gonna hang out here for a while. / 今天真是嘈杂……我要在这清静一会儿。",
        "Pierre": "My store carries the very finest quality products in the whole valley. Please, inspect my grange display closely and see for yourself! / 我的店里有全谷质量最好的商品。请来好好看看我的农庄展览！",
        "Caroline": "Pierre is very serious about his grange display. He's been setting aside the best-looking produce for weeks in preparation. / 皮埃尔非常重视他的农庄展览。他为了准备这个已经预留了好几周最好看的产品。#$e#Hey, best of luck to you if you enter! / 嘿，如果你也参展的话，祝你好运！",
        "Linus": "These animals never judge people by their looks. The same can't be said for humans. / 这些动物不会以貌取人。但是人类就不一样了。",
        "Alex": "I played the 'Strength' game too many times and now my arms feel like rubber. / 我玩了太多次“力量”游戏，现在我的胳膊软得跟橡胶一样。",
        "George": "Hmm... smoked turkey haunch? I guess this festival isn't all bad.$h / 唔……烟熏火鸡腿肉？我想这个庆典并没有那么糟。$h",
        "Evelyn": "I wish Gus would include a vegetarian option. Some zucchini skewers, maybe? / 希望格斯能提供素食套餐。比如来点翠玉瓜串什么的？",
        "Lewis": "Well @, it's the big day... Our most important festival of the year, the 'Stardew Valley Fair'. / 好吧，@，今天是个大日子……我们年度最重要的节日，“星露谷展览会”。#$b#If you'd like to participate by setting up a grange display, I've left an empty stand for you. Just let me know after you've set everything up so we can get to the judging. / 如果您想通过办农庄展览参与其中，我已经为您留了一个空位。在您一切准备完毕后告诉我，这样我们就可以开始评比了。",
        "Clint": "I complain about my job sometimes, but I do take pride in my work. / 我有时会抱怨我的工作，但我还是为我的工作感到自豪。#$b#These are some of my finest pieces. I hope you like them. / 这是一些我最好的作品。希望你喜欢。",
        "Emily": "You know, I would've made a pretty good clown. I think I missed my calling. / 你知道吗，我本会成为一名相当不错的小丑。可我却错过了。",
        "Penny": "I won the wheel of chance ten times in a row and now the man won't let me play anymore...$s / 我连续赢了 10 把幸运转轮，然而现在那个人不让我再玩了……$s",
        "Pam": "Better hurry up, kid... Before ol' Pam here fishes every last lunker out of the tent! Hehe.$h / 最好快点，孩子……在老潘姆来这儿之前把帐篷里所有大鱼都钓走！呵呵。$h",
        "Haley": "Have you been to the fortune teller? She set up her stand in the graveyard. / 你去过占卜师那里吗？她把摊位设在墓地里。#$e#I already saw her... she told me something... interesting. *giggle*$h / 我已经去过了……她告诉我一些……有趣的事。* 咯咯笑 *$h",
        "Jodi": "He doesn't look very happy... I guess Mayor Lewis had to cut costs with a budget clown this year. / 他看起来不开心……我猜镇长刘易斯今年不得不为了削减成本而请了一个廉价的小丑。",
        "Kent": "I'm waiting for this clown to start doing something funny. / 我在等着看小丑的滑稽表演。#$e#Pretty disappointing. / 相当令人失望。",
        "Sam": "Hey @. Having a good time? / 嘿，@。玩得开心吗？#$e#The slingshot tent is pretty fun, and if you get good at it you can really rack up the star tokens. / 弹弓棚超好玩的，如果你擅长这个的话，你可以赚好多星星币。",
        "Leah": "I really admire Robin's carpentry skills. I use a lot of the same techniques in my own line of work. / 我真的很佩服罗宾的木工手艺。我平时干活儿也经常用到。",
        "Shane": "All these animals are friendly and love to get massaged. / 所有这些动物都很友好，并且喜欢被人抚摸。",
        "Marnie": "I tried my best, but my display is pretty weak compared to Pierre's.$s / 我已经尽我所能，但相比皮埃尔，我的展览差远了。$s#$e#Well, maybe the judges will give me bonus points for the massive cheese wheel. / 好吧，也许评委们会因为这一大个奶酪圈给我加分。",
        "Elliott": "I'm trying to get Gus to tell me his sauce recipe, but he won't budge. / 我试图让格斯告诉我他的酱汁的配方，但是他不松口。",
        "Gus": "Eat as much as you like! It's all free today... compliments of Mayor Lewis.$h / 想吃多少就吃多少！今天全部免费……镇长刘易斯的一份心意。$h#$e#Oh! Make sure to dribble some of my secret sauce on there. / 噢！噢！别忘了在上面滴几滴我的秘制酱料。",
        "Dwarf": "You say it's raining up above? *gasp* / 地面上下雨了？*喘气*#$e#Rain... It's almost mythical to us. Some of us live our entire lives without ever experiencing it. / 下雨……这是个很陌生的概念。我们大部分人一辈子都没经历过下雨。",
        "Wizard": "Welwick and I have known each other for a long time... she is a remarkable diviner, and a good friend. / 我和维尔维克认识很久了……她是个出色的占卜师，也是我的好朋友。#$e#... / ……#$e#That clown... I know him from somewhere. / 那个小丑……我在什么地方见过他。#$e#Was it the school of illusion? Or maybe the Carnival of Secrets? Hmm... / 是在幻想学院？还是秘密狂欢节？唔……",
        "Harvey": "And just a few steps over there, Gus is grilling up a batch of pork ribs... Yikes.$s / 离这里几步远的地方，格斯正在烤很多猪排……啊呀。$s#$e#I've got some soul-searching to do...$11 / 我要自我反省一下……$11",
        "Sandy": "I heard it's raining back home. Is that why you came here?$h / 听说家乡在下雨。你是为避雨才跑来这里的吗？$h#$e#I kind of miss the rain, actually...$s / 话说我有点怀念雨景了……$s",
        "Jas": "Ow! A hen pecked my little finger!$u / 嗷！有只母鸡啄了我的小拇指！$u",
        "Vincent": "Moooo! / 哞！",
        "Marlon": "Clint's blades get sharper every year. / 克林特的剑一年比一年锋利。#$e#So do his prices... / 他的价格也是这样……",
        "Willy": "Are you setting up a grange display, @? It's your chance to show off all the good produce from %farm! / 你准备办一个农庄展览吗，@?这是你展示%farm农场里所有好产品的机会！",
        "Leo": "Haha! I've never seen anything like this before...$h / 哈哈！我以前从未见过这样的东西……$h",
        "Abigail_spouse_y2": "Aren't these weapons cool? I might have to bring one of these home with us today.$0 / 这些武器很酷吧？我要不买一把带回家。$0",
        "Leah_spouse_y2": "Hey, Robin is teaching me some innovative techniques this year. / 哎，罗宾今年教了我一些新的技巧。#$e#I'll have to show you later...$1 / 我之后展示给你看……$1",
        "Maru_spouse_y2": "I hope we win the grange display contest! You worked really hard this year. / 希望我们能赢下农庄展览比赛！你今年真的很努力了。",
        "Penny_spouse_y2": "Come here, sit for a while! There's space on the bench for the both of us.$1 / 快来坐一会儿吧！这里还有位置，来，一起坐。$1",
        "Haley_spouse_y2": "It's a little funny seeing Alex stuff his face. He seems to be doing well. / 看亚历克斯狼吞虎咽的，有点滑稽，看来他挺精神的。#$e#I hope we win the grange display contest this year!$1 / 希望今年我们能赢下农庄展览比赛！$1",
        "Emily_spouse_y2": "Sandy traveled all the way from Calico Desert to be here today. / 桑迪今天从卡利科沙漠远道而来。#$b#It's not very often that I get to see her! / 真是稀客！",
        "Sebastian_spouse_y2": "That lady in the graveyard predicted our future...$0 / 那个墓地里的阿姨预测了我们的未来……$0#$b#Apparently, we're destined to live a happy life together.$1 / 她说我们注定会过上幸福的生活。$1",
        "Sam_spouse_y2": "Hey, are you enjoying the festival? I'll be rooting for our grange display!$0 / 哎，你玩得开心吗？咱们的农庄展览我会全力支持的！$0#$e#Psst... If you're going to bet your tokens on the wheel... bet on green!$0 / 悄悄跟你说……如果你要把代币押在转盘上……一定要押绿色！$0",
        "Alex_spouse_y2": "Did you eat yet? There's almost too much to go around!$0 / 你吃过了吗？这都够所有人吃撑了！$0#$e#I already ate three sandwiches... Mmm... that sauce... / 我已经吃了三个三明治了……嗯……那个酱汁……",
        "Harvey_spouse_y2": "Hi, honey. Good luck today in the competition. I just know you're going to shine!$0 / 哎，亲爱的，今天的比赛祝你好运，你一定会大放异彩的！$0",
        "Elliott_spouse_y2": "Victory! I achieved a score of '216' with five fish caught... a new personal best!$1 / 赢了！我钓了五条鱼，得了 216 分……都打破个人记录了！$1#$e#Now, I must choose a fitting prize to purchase for you with these star tokens...$0 / 现在我得用这些星星币买一个合适的奖品送给你……$0",
        "Shane_spouse_y2": "I might ask you to watch the animals soon so I can grab some food.$0 / 我待会儿可能需要你帮我看一下动物，我得去吃点东西。$0",
        "Abigail_y2": "This blade is so elegant. Maybe some day I'll have enough money to buy one!$0 / 这把剑太精美了，等我哪天攒够钱就买一把！$0",
        "Robin_y2": "If you want to master the wood, you have to think like a tree...$0 / 假如你想精通木工，就得学会树木的思考方式……$0",
        "Demetrius_y2": "Sheep have remarkable memory capabilities... retaining familiarity with both fellow sheep and humans...$0 / 羊的记忆力非同寻常……既能记住同伴，也能记得人类……$0#$e#They even form friendships, mirroring the close bonds we humans cultivate with one another!$1 / 它们还会建立友谊，就跟我们人类彼此建立亲密关系一样！$1",
        "Maru_y2": "There's so much to do! I don't know where to begin.$0 / 可以做的事情太多了！我都不知道要先看哪个。$0",
        "Sebastian_y2": "That lady told me my fortune. I don't know what to make of it...$0 / 那个阿姨给我占卜了一下，我不知道该怎么理解……$0",
        "Linus_y2": "Animals are kind of like little people... they also have feelings and emotions.$0 / 动物有点像小孩子……它们也有情感和想法。$0",
        "Pierre_y2": "I'm confident that I'll emerge victorious in this year's grange display competition!$1 / 我有信心在今年的农庄展览比赛中脱颖而出！$1",
        "Caroline_y2": "Some of the produce in our grange display came from my little greenhouse. We've been carefully growing this stuff all year!$0 / 我们的农庄展览品里有一些是在我的温室种出来的，我们精心照料一整年了！$0",
        "Alex_y2": "Every hundred rounds of the strength game I win, I eat another BBQ sandwich.$0 / 我每赢一百局力量测试游戏，就吃一个烤肉三明治。$0",
        "George_y2": "%George is on the verge of falling asleep. / %乔治快要睡着了。",
        "Evelyn_y2": "Hee hee... Maybe I should start a collection of clown figurines... / 嘻嘻……也许我可以开始收藏小丑雕像……",
        "Lewis_y2": "Greetings, @! The 'Stardew Valley Fair' is finally here and the crowd is growing by the minute. / @，你好！“星露谷集市”终于开始了，大家都蜂拥而至。#$b#Just like last year, I've set up an empty grange display for you. Speak with me when you're ready to commence the judging. / 和去年一样，我给你准备了一个农庄展示的空位，你准备好开始评分了就来跟我说。",
        "Clint_y2": "It's heartening to see others take an interest in my work. Makes me feel like I'm doing something good in the world. / 看到别人对我的成果感兴趣，真是令人振奋，让我感觉我在做有益的事情。#$e#I finished some of these pieces just last week. Please inspect them closely, I stand behind my work! / 有几件是我上周才完成的。来仔细看看吧，我就站在这后面！",
        "Penny_y2": "*phew* After being on my feet all day, it's nice to finally take a moment to relax.$0 / 呼……我忙碌了一天，终于可以放松一下了。$0",
        "Pam_y2": "Life don't get much better than this, kid!$1 / 孩子，这生活真是太好了！$1",
        "Emily_y2": "When Sandy and I were kids, we joked about running away from it all and joining the circus.$0 / 小时候我跟桑迪在一起玩，我们开玩笑说要逃离一切，去加入马戏团。$0#$e#I don't think we would've actually gone through with it, but it's fun to imagine.$1 / 我觉得我们即使真的去了也坚持不了，不过想象一下还是很快乐的。$1",
        "Haley_y2": "I'm trying to maintain a diet this fall... but I can't resist these juicy burgers!$h / 今年秋天我是想减肥的……但这些汉堡太诱人了，我实在忍不住！$h",
        "Jodi_y2": "Oh no. Who's responsible for littering here?$2 / 唉，这是谁扔的垃圾？$2#$e#Every year we get some tourists that don't respect our town...$2 / 每年都有游客不尊重我们小镇……$2",
        "Kent_y2": "*chuckle* My son has a knack for accuracy. I wonder if he got it from me.$1 / 呵呵，我儿子的准头很好，不知道是不是遗传我的。$1",
        "Marlon_y2": "I'm in the market for a new weapon. I wonder if I could negotiate a trade with Clint... / 我想买一把新武器，要不要跟克林特谈一笔生意呢……",
        "Sam_y2": "Ugh... I gambled and lost it all to the spinning wheel...$2 / 唉……我在转盘上输光了……$2#$e#I should've went with green.$0 / 早知道就押绿色了。$0",
        "Leah_y2": "I think Robin and I make a pretty good team, don't you think? / 我觉得我跟罗宾组队真的很强，你觉得呢？",
        "Shane_y2": "The animals have been given their favorite foods, so they're happy.$h / 动物们吃了最喜欢的东西，所以很开心。$h#$e#Feel free to pet them, they won't bite. / 可以随便摸，不会咬人的。",
        "Marnie_y2": "My animals had a successful year! I'm hoping the high-quality produce will impress the judges.$1 / 我的动物们今年状态很不错！希望高品质的产品能打动评委。$1#$e#How's your grange display, @? It's your moment to showcase the fruits of your labor.$0 / @，你的农庄展览怎么样了？现在正是展示劳动成果的时候。$0",
        "Elliott_y2": "Ah, don't mind the smell... I just emerged from the fishing booth with a sizable haul!$1 / 啊，可能有点鱼腥味，不好意思……我刚刚从钓鱼摊位出来，收获颇丰！$1#$e#Now, I must decide what to do with all these star tokens...$0 / 现在我得想想，这么多星星币要用来做些什么……$0",
        "Gus_y2": "Working four grills simultaneously is hard work! There's a large and hungry crowd to cater to today.$0 / 同时操作四个烤架真累啊！今天有一大群饥肠辘辘的人要招待。$0#$e#I put a little dash of my zesty sauce in each patty. *wink* / 我在肉饼里都加了我的特制风味酱。（眨眼暗示）",
        "Dwarf_y2": "I was curious about this human gathering... $0 / 我对人类集会有点好奇……$0#$e#Please don't tell anyone. I'm hoping to remain hidden here...$0 / 请不要跟别人说，我想隐藏身份……$0",
        "Wizard_y2": "If you wish to peer through the mists of tomorrow, speak to my colleague Welwick.$0 / 如果你想窥破未来的迷雾，就去找我的同行维尔维克谈谈吧。$0#$b#She has an uncommon gift... / 她有非同寻常的天赋……#$e#That young man by the tree seemed intrigued by his reading, but even with my powers, I cannot probe the innermost secrets of the heart...$0 / 树下的那个年轻人看书看得好像很认真，不过以我的能力都无法探测到他内心最深处的秘密……$0",
        "Harvey_y2": "I'm astonished by the level of craftsmanship on display here. Some people are so talented!$0 / 这些展示品实在是手艺高超，有才的人真多啊！$0",
        "Sandy_y2": "The Stardew Valley community is truly one-of-a-kind...$0 / 星露谷真是独一无二的……$0",
        "Jas_y2": "Mooo! Moooooo!$1 / 哞！哞哞！$1#$e#I'm trying to talk to the baby cows.$0 / 我在尝试和小牛说话。$0",
        "Vincent_y2": "Can I play the slingshot game again, Dad!? Please?$0 / 爸爸，我能再玩一次弹弓游戏吗？求求你了！$0",
        "Willy_y2": "I managed to catch several iridium-quality beauties, just in time for this year's fair!$1 / 我钓到了几条铱星品质的好东西，正好能赶上今年的集市！$1#$e#After our grange displays are judged I'll have to try my hand at the fishing game tent.$0 / 农庄展览评分出来之后，我要去钓鱼游戏的帐篷玩玩看。$0",
        "Leo_y2": "I'm making friends with these birds!$1 / 我在和鸟儿交朋友呢！$1"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Festivals/fall27",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "name": "Spirit's Eve / 万灵节",
        "Abigail_spouse": "You'll have to tell me what's beyond, I can't go on... spiders...$s / 你能告诉我更远处有什么吗？我没法继续了……蜘蛛……$s",
        "Leah_spouse": "I may have had a little too much pumpkin ale... / 我可能喝多了点南瓜酒……",
        "Maru_spouse": "I'm confused... you go on ahead and let me figure this out. / 我已经懵了……你继续走吧，让我自己解决。",
        "Penny_spouse": "Oh... These vapors... Hmmm... You look nice tonight.$l / 噢！这些水气……唔……今晚你看起来不错。$l",
        "Haley_spouse": "I get scared easily... I think I'm just going to stay right here.$s / 我很容易变得害怕……我想我还是留在这儿好了。$s",
        "Sebastian_spouse": "It would be interesting to have one of these on the farm. / 在农场里养一个这样的东西肯定会很有趣。",
        "Sam_spouse": "Hey, I was wondering when you'd show up!$h / 嘿，我正找你呢！$h",
        "Harvey_spouse": "Hi... I was hoping you'd find me here...$l / 你好……我希望你能在这里找到我……$l",
        "Elliott_spouse": "Mmph... I believe I've eaten a few too many slices of pumpkin pie. / 嗯……我想我吃了太多的南瓜派了。",
        "Abigail": "I can't go on... spiders...$s / 我不能继续了……蜘蛛……$s",
        "Robin": "Well, winter's almost here. It's a great time to stockpile wood and stone. / 嗯，冬季就要来了。现在是囤积木材和石头的绝佳时机。",
        "Demetrius": "I haven't seen Maru in hours... I hope she's alright. / 我已经几小时没有看到玛鲁了……希望她没事。",
        "Maru": "I think I've already been this way... no, wait...$s / 我好像走过这条路……不，等等……$s#$e#I'm lost...$s / 我迷路了……$s",
        "Sebastian": "I have no idea how these skeletons are walking... creepy. / 我不知道这些骷髅是怎么走起来的……太吓人了。#$e#It's pretty cool though. / 虽然这样很酷。",
        "Caroline": "I get scared very easily. I'll leave the haunted maze to the younger people. / 我很胆小的。我会把闹鬼迷宫留给年轻人的。",
        "Linus": "Good show, old friend. / 做得好，老朋友。",
        "Alex": "There's something weird over there. But how do I get to it? / 那边好像在发生什么大事。好像过去看看哦。#$e#There's gotta be a secret passage somewhere around here. / 这附近一定有什么秘密通道。",
        "George": "Hmm... smoked turkey haunch? I guess this festival isn't all bad.$h / 唔……烟熏火鸡腿肉？我想这个庆典并没有那么糟。$h",
        "Evelyn": "I wish Gus would include a vegetarian option. Some zucchini skewers, maybe? / 希望格斯能提供素食套餐。比如来点翠玉瓜串什么的？",
        "Lewis": "Good evening, @. Have you ventured into the haunted maze yet? It's quite spooky. / 晚上好，@。你进过那个闹鬼迷宫没？那里好恐怖哦。#$e#That strange man who lives in the tower set it all up himself. He wouldn't let anyone near while he was working on it. / 那个住在塔里的怪人搞得这么吓人。他在布置迷宫时还故作神秘不让人靠近。",
        "Clint": "One of my iridium-infused maces would make quick work of these things. / 如果用我的铱制锤肯定能马上搞定它们。",
        "Emily": "Do you like the jack-o-lanterns? I carved them myself. / 你喜欢南瓜灯吗？这是我自己雕的。",
        "Penny": "The vapor from this cauldron... it's making my head spin, but I can't seem to leave...$u / 这口锅冒出来的蒸汽……熏得我头昏脑涨，想离开都没力……$u",
        "Pam": "I'll come to any event with free grub! You won't see me in the haunted maze, though. / 凡是有免费食物可以吃吃吃的活动我都会去！不过闹鬼迷宫什么的就别算上我了。",
        "Haley": "Eek! I'm too scared.$s / 哇！吓死我了。$s",
        "Jodi": "Vincent's upset that I won't let him go into the haunted maze... but he's just a little boy! / 文森特很生气我不让他去闹鬼迷宫……但是小孩子真的不适合去！",
        "Kent": "Hey, @. Nice evening, isn't it? / 嘿，@。今晚天色不错。",
        "Sam": "That's odd... It's just a dead end up ahead. / 奇怪……前面无路可走了。#$e#I could've sworn there was someone ahead of me when I went through the maze, though. Where'd they go? / 可是刚才进迷宫时是有人走在我前面的啊。他们人呢？",
        "Leah": "Mm, hi. Sorry... mouth full of blackberries. / 唔，嗨。我在吃着黑莓……不是很方便说话。",
        "Marnie": "Hi, @. Have you had a productive fall? / 您好，@。这个秋天收成如何？#$e#It's starting to get quite cold... crops won't hold out for much longer. / 天气越来越冷了……农作物都快要枯萎了。",
        "Elliott": "Why, hello @. It's chilly, isn't it? / 哈喽，@。天气好冷啊，对不？",
        "Gus": "It's a lot of fun to cook with pumpkin. Such an interesting fruit. / 南瓜可以搭配出很多种煮法。真是一种有趣的蔬菜。",
        "Dwarf": "You say it's raining up above? *gasp* / 地面上下雨了？*喘气*#$e#Rain... It's almost mythical to us. Some of us live our entire lives without ever experiencing it. / 下雨……这是个很陌生的概念。我们大部分人一辈子都没经历过下雨。",
        "Wizard": "The affairs of mundane folk matter little to me, but the elementals like a chance to see you up close. / 尘世间的俗事我不关心，但是元素们想要近距离观察你们。#$e#It was for them that I created this silly maze. / 所以我才花心机打造这个无聊的迷宫。",
        "Harvey": "Oh! You found me...$8 / 噢！被你发现了……$8#$b#The truth is, I got too scared so I came here to hide. Don't tell anyone.$s / 其实，我是太慌张才躲到这里来的。你别告诉任何人。$s",
        "Shane": "Why is there no more pumpkin ale? / 南瓜啤酒怎么都没了？",
        "Sandy": "I heard it's raining back home. Is that why you came here?$h / 听说家乡在下雨。你是为避雨才跑来这里的吗？$h#$e#I kind of miss the rain, actually...$s / 话说我有点怀念雨景了……$s",
        "Jas": "But Aunt Marnie! I wanna go in the maze! I'm not scared!$s / 玛妮阿姨！我想进去迷宫玩嘛！我不怕！$s",
        "Vincent": "Mother won't let me go in the maze. *sob*$s / 妈妈不让我进迷宫。*呜咽*$s",
        "Marlon": "Don't get too close to the cage. / 不要太靠近笼子。",
        "Leo": "%Leo's unblinking eyes are glued to the screen. You're unable to get his attention. / %雷欧目不转睛地盯着屏幕。你无法吸引他的注意。",
        "Abigail_spouse_y2": "Have you ever fought any of these monsters before?$0 / 你之前打过这些怪物吗？$0#$e#Even... the s-spiders?$2 / 蜘、蜘蛛……也打过？$2",
        "Leah_spouse_y2": "I probably had too much pumpkin ale before jumping into the maze.$2 / 我进迷宫之前好像喝太多南瓜啤酒了。$2#$e#You go on ahead. I'll catch up.$0 / 你先进去吧，我会跟上的。$0",
        "Maru_spouse_y2": "Grab a plate and sit down with the family!$1 / 拿点吃的，咱们坐一会儿吧！$1",
        "Penny_spouse_y2": "*phew* I got lost in the maze...$3 / 呼……我在迷宫里迷路了……$3#$e#I was worried I might get trapped and everyone would go home without me!$12 / 我很担心被困住之后，大家会丢下我各自回家！$12",
        "Emily_spouse_y2": "*giggle* I knew you'd find your way here.$0 / 嘿嘿……我知道你会走到这里的。$0",
        "Haley_spouse_y2": "Hah! None of this is real.$h / 哈！这里的东西全都是假的。$h#$b#.... right, @? It's not real... right?$12 / ……@，是不是啊？都是假的……吧？$12",
        "Alex_spouse_y2": "Hey, you made it past the creepy hands.$1 / 哎，你闯过了那几个渗人的手。$1#$e#I think I hear someone calling for help nearby.$0 / 我好像听到附近有人在喊救命。$0",
        "Sebastian_spouse_y2": "Hey, could you... give me a hand? Hehehe...$h / 来……把你的手……也给我……嘻嘻嘻……$h#$e#These gravestones would look nice on the farm, don't you think?$0 / 这几块墓碑挺好看的，要不要在农场上放几块？$0",
        "Sam_spouse_y2": "My little brother and I made it pretty far in here but we got stuck. / 我跟我弟弟已经走得很深了，不过还是进了死胡同。#$e#You go on ahead... find that treasure for us! / 你先走吧……记得替我们找到宝藏！",
        "Harvey_spouse_y2": "I was wondering when I'd see you.$1 / 我还在想你什么时候来。$1#$e#Don't mind me. I'm just taking a quick breather.$0 / 不用管我，我就稍微喘口气。$0",
        "Elliott_spouse_y2": "I shudder to think what would happen if these got loose...%noturn$2 / 我不敢想象如果怪物逃出来会怎么样……%noturn$2#$e#Fear not, my dear! I would run the cursed wretch through, before it could lay a finger on you. / 亲爱的，不必害怕！我会捅穿这该死的混蛋，不会让它伤到你一根毫毛。",
        "Shane_spouse_y2": "I talked Marnie into letting me take Jas into the maze. I think she's old enough.$0 / 我说服了玛妮让我带贾斯进迷宫转转，我觉得她也不小了。$0#$e#We're going very slow, though. Go ahead without us!$1 / 不过我们会慢慢走，你先进去吧！$1",
        "Abigail_y2": "Did you see the decorations on our house? I don't like it...$2 / 你看到我家房子上的装饰了吗？我不喜欢……$2",
        "Robin_y2": "Are you looking forward to things slowing down soon? Winter is around the corner.$0 / 你在期待生活的节奏慢下来吗？冬天马上就要到了。$0",
        "Demetrius_y2": "Did you know... a study in the Journal of Anthropological Physiology found that the cadence, tempo, and key of music can have a measurable impact on cortisol levels? / 你知道吗……《人类生理学杂志》上的一项研究发现，音乐的终止式、速度、调性对皮质醇水平有显著影响。#$e#Er... Is there vanilla ice cream to go with the blackberry cobbler?$0 / 呃……有香草冰淇淋吗？我想配着黑莓馅饼吃。$0",
        "Maru_y2": "After I finish this food, I'm going head-first into that maze!$0 / 等我吃完之后，肯定要一头扎进那个迷宫！$0",
        "Sebastian_y2": "This is my spot.$0 / 这是我的地盘。$0",
        "Pierre_y2": "Ah, it's farmer @! I have quite the selection of wares tonight. Take a look!$0 / 啊，@，你来啦！今晚我这有很多好东西，来看看吧！$0",
        "Caroline_y2": "I should make a plate of food for my husband. He's been manning the shop all night.$0 / 我应该给我老公弄点吃的，他整完都在看着铺子。$0",
        "Linus_y2": "Haha! Another fine creation, my old friend.$1 / 哈哈！老朋友，你这又是一个杰作。$1",
        "Alex_y2": "I think I heard a girl screaming... She needs my help!$0 / 我好像听到有女生在尖叫……我得去帮她！$0",
        "George_y2": "If I wasn't in this blasted chair, I'd be running circles around everyone in that maze!$0 / 要不是因为这个破轮椅，我早就在迷宫里通关几百回了！$0",
        "Evelyn_y2": "Dear, can you pass the zucchini fritters please?$0 / 亲爱的，你能把油炸西葫芦递给我吗？$0",
        "Lewis_y2": "Good evening, @. Once again, we've been graced with a haunted maze, constructed in secret by the eccentric who lives out in the forest.$0 / @，晚上好。住在森林里面的那个怪人又神神秘秘地给我们造了一个闹鬼迷宫。$0#$e#I've heard it's larger this year. Good luck if you dare to venture inside... / 听说今年的迷宫更大了，如果你有勇气进去的话，祝你好运……",
        "Clint_y2": "I already made it through the maze... now it's time to kick back with a pumpkin ale! / 我已经通过迷宫了……该喝点南瓜啤酒放松一下了！#$e#...I'm trying my best to ignore the spider infestation behind me.$0 / ……我在尽可能无视我身后的蜘蛛群。$0",
        "Emily_y2": "Ooooh. You found the secret entrance too!$1 / 哦哦，你也找到了秘密入口了！$1",
        "Penny_y2": "I was in the maze for a while but then I got hungry.$0 / 我进迷宫看了一会儿，后来肚子饿了。$0#$e#My Mom seems to be enjoying herself.$0 / 我妈好像兴致很高。$0",
        "Pam_y2": "Pass another bottle of pumpkin ale over here!... *hic*$1 / 再来一瓶一瓶南瓜啤酒！……嗝……$1",
        "Haley_y2": "Have you seen my sister?$2 / 你看到我姐姐了吗？$2#$e#Emily! Can you hear me?$2 / 艾米丽！你在哪里？$2",
        "Jodi_y2": "Sam took Vincent into the maze. I hope they're okay...$0 / 山姆带着文森特进迷宫去了，希望他们没事……$0",
        "Kent_y2": "These things don't look so tough.$0 / 这些玩意儿看起来也不是很强啊。$0",
        "Sam_y2": "Am I Sam? Heh, heh, heh...$11 / 从今天起我就是山姆了，嘻、嘻、嘻……$11",
        "Leah_y2": "Is it this way? Or maybe over here?$0 / 要走这边吗？还是那边？$0",
        "Marnie_y2": "I hope Jas is okay in there.$2 / 希望贾斯在那里面没事。$2#$e#Did you have a successful year farming, @? / @，你今年的收成怎么样？",
        "Elliott_y2": "Oh pitiful wretch... in what fetid grotto lies your kingdom?%noturn$0 / 啊，可悲的混蛋……哪一个腐臭的洞窟才是你的王国？%noturn$0#$e#Sometimes, one must stare into the abyss to stir a languid muse... / 有时候，你必须凝视深渊，才能唤醒慵懒的缪斯女神……",
        "Gus_y2": "Carving pumpkins is a talent of mine. I usually do most of the Jack-O-Lanterns for everyone in town. / 我很擅长雕刻南瓜，镇上绝大部分南瓜灯都是我做的。#$b#All I ask in return is to keep the seeds... sprinkle a little cinnamon sugar on those puppies and you've got yourself a golden snack!$h / 我只要求把南瓜籽留给我……撒上一点肉桂糖，可好吃了！$h",
        "Dwarf_y2": "This place is very strange...$0 / 这个地方好奇怪……$0",
        "Wizard_y2": "The trials continue... Every magician must have an apprentice... / 考验仍在继续……每个魔法师都必须有一个学徒……",
        "Harvey_y2": "I'm afraid to say I'm quite puzzled on this one...$0 / 很遗憾，我现在非常困惑……$0",
        "Shane_y2": "You gotta stay close to me, Jas. Don't run off!%noturn$0 / 贾斯，你得跟紧我，别走丢了！%noturn$0",
        "Jas_y2": "Let's go this way!%noturn$1 / 我们走这边！%noturn$1",
        "Willy_y2": "I'd watch yer back, lad... something terrible's in that maze... / 小伙子，多留神……迷宫里有可怕的东西……^I'd watch yer back, miss... something terrible's in that maze... / 小姑娘，多留神……迷宫里有可怕的东西……",
        "Vincent_y2": "Did we beat the maze? Where's my prize?$0 / 我们通过迷宫了吗？奖品在哪里？$0",
        "Marlon_y2": "I caught more monsters this year. Mind your distance near the cages. / 我今年抓到了更多怪物，注意离笼子远点。",
        "Leo_y2": "This is a maze inside of a maze... My head is spinning...$0 / 迷宫里怎么还有一个迷宫……我头好晕……$0",
        "Krobus_y2": "Wh-what are you doing here?$0 / 你、你在这里干什么？$0"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Festivals/winter8",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "name": "Festival of Ice / 冰雪节",
        "mainEvent": "globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/playMusic none/warpFarmers 71 35 0 72 35 0 70 35 0 69 35 0 73 35 0 71 36 0 70 36 0 72 36 0 69 36 0 73 36 0 left 73 37 0/loadActors Main-Event/faceDirection Pam 1/faceDirection Elliott 0/faceDirection Willy 0/viewport 71 35 true/pause 2000/speak Lewis \"Alright, everyone. Let's begin this year's ice fishing competition. / 大家好，今年的冰钓比赛即将开始。\"/pause 200/faceDirection Lewis 3/pause 300/faceDirection Lewis 2/faceDirection Lewis 1/pause 300/faceDirection Lewis 2/pause 400/speak Lewis \"Contestants, your goal is to catch as many fish as you possibly can in two minutes using the provided fishing rods. / 各位选手，你们的目标是在两分钟内用指定的钓具钓上尽可能多的鱼。#$b#You must catch your fish here, from these holes in the ice. / 鱼必须是从这些冰洞里钓上来的。\"/pause 600/speak Lewis \"Well, is everyone ready? / 都准备好了吗？\"/pause 500/waitForOtherPlayers startContest/jump Lewis/faceDirection Pam 2 true/faceDirection Elliott 1 true/faceDirection Willy 2 true/speak Lewis \"Begin! / 开始！\"/advancedMove Lewis false 0 -4 2 1000/advancedMove Marnie true 4 6000 -2 0 4 5000 2 0/advancedMove Maru true 3 4000 0 2 3 7000 0 -2/advancedMove Jas true 2 0 0 -9 -4 0 2 20000 4 0 0 9 -2 0 3 15000/advancedMove Jodi true 1 6000 -1 0 0 2 1 8000 0 -1 1 6000 0 -1 1 0/jump Willy/shake Pam 700/showFrame Pam 16/extendSourceRect Pam 0 32/showFrame Elliott 40/extendSourceRect Elliott 16 0/shake Elliott 400/pause 300/showFrame Willy 16/extendSourceRect Willy 0 32/playMusic fallFest/playerControl iceFishing",
        "afterIceFishing": "pause 100/playSound whistle/waitForOtherPlayers endContest/pause 1000/restoreStashedItem/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/extendSourceRect Pam reset/extendSourceRect Willy reset/extendSourceRect Elliott reset/specificTemporarySprite iceFishingCatch/faceDirection Pam 0/faceDirection Willy 0/faceDirection Elliott 0/playMusic event1/warpFarmers 71 35 0 72 35 0 70 35 0 69 35 0 73 35 0 71 36 0 70 36 0 72 36 0 69 36 0 73 36 0 left 73 37 0/pause 1000/viewport 71 35 true/pause 2000/move Lewis 0 4 2/speak Lewis \"Wow, that's a lot of fish!$h / 哇，这么多鱼！$h\"/pause 300/showFrame Lewis 18/shake Lewis 1000/speak Lewis \"*gag*... the smell...$s / *呕*……这味道……$s\"/pause 500/showFrame Lewis 0/pause 600/move Lewis 0 1 2/speak Lewis \"Now, for the winner of this year's ice fishing competition... / 咳，本届冰钓比赛的胜利者会获得……\"/pause 800/playMusic none/pause 3000/cutscene iceFishingWinner/null/playMusic event1/pause 500/fork DickWin/move Lewis 0 1 2/speak Lewis \"Here's your prize! Enjoy. / 这是你的奖品！祝贺你。\"/awardFestivalPrize/null/move Lewis 0 -1 0/speak Lewis \"Well, that's it for this year's Festival of Ice. Thanks for coming, everyone!  / 好了，今年的冰雪节到此为止！谢谢大家的光临！#$b#Now let's release these poor fish...$s / 现在快把那些可怜的鱼儿放生吧……$s\"/move Lewis -3 0 0/move Lewis 0 -1 0/advancedMove Willy true 0 3 -2 0/pause 600/viewport move 1 0 5000/pause 2000/playMusic none/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 1000/cutscene iceFishingWinnerMP/fork OtherPlayerWin/message \"I can't believe I won! Well, time to head home. / 我居然赢了，难以置信！该回家了。\"/waitForOtherPlayers festivalEnd/end",
        "OtherPlayerWin": "message \"I didn't win the competition, but it was still fun! Time to head home.\"/waitForOtherPlayers festivalEnd/end / message \"我没有赢得比赛，但还是很好玩！该回家了。\"/waitForOtherPlayers festivalEnd/end",
        "DickWin": "pause 100/jump Willy/faceDirection Elliott 3/pause 800/move Willy 0 -1 0/faceDirection Elliott 0/speak Lewis \"Here's your prize, Willy. Enjoy. / 这是你的奖品，威利。尽情享受吧\"/pause 500/move Willy 0 -2 0/move Lewis -1 0 2/move Lewis 0 1 2/playSound coin/pause 400/move Lewis 0 -1 0/pause 500/speak Lewis \"Well, that's it for this year's Festival of Ice. Thanks for coming, everyone! / 好的，今年的冰雪节到此为止！谢谢大家的光临！#$b#Now let's release these poor fish...$s / 现在快把那些可怜的鱼儿放生吧……$s\"/move Lewis -2 0 0/pause 600/viewport move 1 0 5000/pause 2000/playMusic none/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 1000/message \"I didn't win the competition, but it was still fun! Time to head home. / 我没有赢得比赛，但还是很好玩！该回家了。\"/waitForOtherPlayers festivalEnd/end",
        "Abigail_spouse": "Hey, honey... look, it's you!$h / 嘿，亲爱的……看，是你哦！$h",
        "Penny_spouse": "Are you entering the fishing contest this year, @? My mom's pretty serious about winning. / 你今年打算参加钓鱼大赛吗，@？我妈对今年的比赛志在必得。",
        "Haley_spouse": "Brr... my hands are freezing from making this snowman.$l / 啊……我堆雪人堆得手都冻僵了。$l",
        "Sebastian_spouse": "Don't worry about me, I never get cold... / 别担心，我从不会感冒的……",
        "Sam_spouse": "Aren't you cold? Are you sure you don't want my jacket? / 你不冷吗？真的不要披上我的外套吗？",
        "Alex_spouse": "I'll be rooting for you in the fishing competition. / 我看好你赢得这次的钓鱼比赛。",
        "Harvey_spouse": "I'm dreaming of our warm fire back home...$l / 我在想念着家里那温暖的炉火……$l",
        "Elliott_spouse": "I know you'll beat me in the fishing competition, but I don't mind. I'm just here for the fun of it.$h / 我知道这次的钓鱼比赛肯定会输给你，不过我不介意。我只是来体验参与的乐趣。$h",
        "Abigail": "What do you think of my snow-goon? / 你觉得我的雪怪怎么样？",
        "Robin": "I'm sorry, but carving ice parapets requires my undivided attention! / 抱歉，我得全心全意去雕刻这冰墙！",
        "Demetrius": "You know what? I probably should've worn a jacket. / 唉，早知道就该穿上外套出门。",
        "Maru": "I'm not very creative when it comes to snowmen.$s / 我堆雪人不是很在行。$s",
        "Sebastian": "Cold? Nah, I never get cold. / 冷吗？不，我从不会感冒的。",
        "Pierre": "This snow is so cold I can't feel my fingers anymore...$s / 这场雪好冷，我手指都冻麻了……$s",
        "Shane": "If it was up to me, I'd probably have a pizza festival at the saloon, instead... / 要我来说的话，我肯定会在酒吧举行一场披萨节庆，而不是……",
        "Caroline": "How's winter coming along for you, @?$h / 这冬天过得还好吗，@？$h",
        "Linus": "Igloo-building's an art I picked up from the tundra dwellers who live beyond the frozen sea. / 圆顶冰屋这种设计是我从海外冻原居民那里学习回来的。#$e#That was many years ago.$h / 都是多年前的事了。$h#$e#An Igloo makes a nice home, but it's easier to just stay in my tent year-round. / 圆顶冰屋是个很舒适的房子，但我还是比较喜欢住在帐篷里。",
        "Alex": "Snowmen are okay, I guess. But mostly I'm looking forward to the spring. / 雪人挺好玩的。但我还是更喜欢春天。",
        "George": "Hmmph... Wife dragged me out into the cold for this? / 啊……老婆大冬天把我拽出来就是为了这玩意？",
        "Evelyn": "Did I ever tell you how George and I first met? He actually pelted me with a snowball in this very festival. / 你知道我和乔治是怎么认识的吗？他就是在这一天扔雪球时不小心砸中我。#$e#He was a gentleman back then, and came over to see if I was okay.$h / 他那时候还是很绅士的，还跑过来问我有没有受伤。$h",
        "Lewis": "Welcome to the Festival of Ice! / 欢迎来到冰雪节！#$e#The highlight of today's festival is the ice fishing competition. We set up this 'frozen lake' and stocked it full of fish. / 今天的重头戏是冰钓比赛！我们做了这个“冰冻之湖”并且在水中放满了鱼。#$b#Just let me know when you're ready to compete. / 你要是准备好了那就告诉我。",
        "Clint": "Emily started helping me without any provocation... does that mean something? *gulp*$4 / 艾米丽突然变得那么热心地帮助我……难道是意味着？*吞口水*……$4",
        "Emily": "Wow, this snowman needs a makeover. Who made this?$s / 哇塞，这个雪人堆得那么丑。是谁的杰作？$s",
        "Penny": "$y 'Hmm... What kind of snowman should we make?_A classic one. Carrot nose, top-hat, scarf._I guess maybe it's best to stick with the classics, huh?$h_Something funky. Icicle antennas, pine cone eyes._Okay! That sounds like fun.$h_Snowmen are boring. Think outside of the box!_Um, okay... I think I might stick with something more conventional.' / $y '唔……要做个什么样的雪人好呢？_传统的雪人。胡萝卜鼻子、高帽子、围巾。_我想还是保持传统比较好，对吧？$h_有趣一点的。冰柱触角、松果眼睛。_对！这样才比较有意思。$h_雪人太没意思了，咱们不要思想僵化！_呃，好吧……我还是觉得保守一点好。'",
        "Pam": "I plan on winning the ice fishing competition! / 我想赢得冰钓比赛！#$e#Willy is gonna be pretty hard to beat, though... He does this kinda stuff day and night.$s / 可是威利不是吃素的……钓鱼对他来说是家常便饭。$s",
        "Haley": "I guess Winter isn't all bad... playing in the snow can be fun! / 冬天也不是想象中那么的糟糕……在雪中玩耍也挺有意思的！",
        "Jodi": "The forest looks beautiful in the winter, doesn't it? / 冬天的森林看起来很美，对不？",
        "Kent": "I like winter. It's peaceful. / 我喜欢冬天。很宁静。",
        "Sam": "Hey, @. Are you gonna enter the ice fishing competition? / 嘿，@。想参加冰钓比赛不？#$e#Oh, not me. I don't know how to fish. / 我？我不行。我不会钓鱼的。",
        "Leah": "Oh, ice. A beautiful material to sculpt in, but so impermanent. / 冰，是种优秀的雕刻材料，可惜它不能长存。#$e#But I guess that might make the art even better. / 不过短暂而美丽的东西才更有艺术的气息。",
        "Marnie": "I feel bad for all the poor, cold animals out there.$s / 我替外面那些又冷又饿的动物默哀。$s",
        "Elliott": "I'm entering the ice fishing competition today. Why not? / 我今天要去参加冰钓比赛。男子汉大丈夫，有什么好怕的？#$e#It's rare that Willy ever loses, though. / 不过想战胜威利的确是很困难的。",
        "Gus": "Sorry there's no food. / 抱歉这儿没有吃的。#$e#Just wait until the Feast of the Winter Star. You'll be stuffed for days. / 请等待冬日星盛宴吧。保证你到时候吃到撑。",
        "Willy": "$y 'Hey, @. Ready for some ice fishing?_Yes. I'll do my best!_That's the spirit!$h_Yes, and I'm going to beat you!_We'll see.$h_To be honest, no. I'm bad at fishing._Well, then think of it as good practice!$h' / $y '嘿，@。准备好去冰钓了吗？_是的。我会全力以赴！_要的就是这股精神！$h_是的，而且我会战胜你的！_那就拭目以待咯。$h_讲真，我没有信心。我钓鱼技术很烂。_那就当作一场训练呗！$h'",
        "Wizard": "Sneaking off to visit my weird tower? You're odd for a mundane. / 偷偷溜出来看我的怪塔？你这人真是非比寻常。",
        "Harvey": "Extreme temperatures can put your body under a lot of stress, so make sure to bundle up! / 极端的寒冷会使身体饱受折磨，所以别忘了要穿得暖和暖和的！#$e#Oh, and enjoy the festival!$h / 对了，节日快乐！$h",
        "Sandy": "I heard it's raining back home. Is that why you came here?$h / 听说家乡在下雨。你是为避雨才跑来这里的吗？$h#$e#I kind of miss the rain, actually...$s / 话说我有点怀念雨景了……$s",
        "Jas": "I wanna give him a carrot nose!$h / 我想给他添加个胡萝卜鼻子！$h",
        "Vincent": "I saw a big fish down there! / 我看见那边有条大鱼！",
        "Marlon": "Hey, good afternoon. / 嗨，下午好。",
        "Leo": "You could make an igloo twice as warm if you stuffed feathers in the walls! / 如果你在冰屋的墙里塞满羽毛，会暖和很多！",
        "mainEvent_y2": "globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/playMusic none/warpFarmers 71 35 0 69 36 0 70 35 0 69 35 0 73 35 0 71 36 0 70 36 0 72 37 0 69 36 0 73 36 0 left 73 37 0/loadActors Main-Event/faceDirection Pam 0/faceDirection Elliott 1/faceDirection Willy 3/positionOffset Harvey 12 24/viewport 71 35 true/pause 2000/speak Lewis \"Alright, everyone. Let's begin this year's ice fishing competition. / 大家好，今年的冰钓比赛即将开始。\"/pause 200/faceDirection Lewis 3/pause 300/faceDirection Lewis 2/faceDirection Lewis 1/pause 300/faceDirection Lewis 2/pause 400/speak Lewis \"Contestants, with the provided fishing rods you must catch as many fish as you can from these holes in the ice. / 各位选手，你们要用指定的钓具，从冰洞里钓上尽可能多的鱼。\"/pause 600/speak Lewis \"Are you all ready? / 都准备好了吗？\"/pause 500/waitForOtherPlayers startContest/jump Lewis/faceDirection Pam 2 true/faceDirection Elliott 1 true/faceDirection Willy 2 true/speak Lewis \"Begin! / 开始！\"/advancedMove Lewis false 0 -4 2 1000/advancedMove Maru true 3 3000 4 300 0 -3 4 250 3 6400 2 300 0 3 2 300 3 4250/advancedMove Vincent true 2 6500 1 300 3 0 1 300 2 7400 3 300 -3 0 3 300 2 1000/advancedMove Penny true 4 5750 3 300 -5 0 3 300 4 6100 1 300 5 0 1 300 4 1000/advancedMove Clint false 4 6000 1 1500 4 4000 1 2000 1 0 0 -1 4 15000 1 2000 4 1000/advancedMove Emily false 4 17000 3 1750 4 4000 1 350 2 0 0 -2 1 0 1 250 4 250 3 5000/advancedMove Jas true 1 4500 4 5750/advancedMove Abigail true 1 8400 2 3650/jump Willy/shake Pam 700/showFrame Pam 16/extendSourceRect Pam 0 32/showFrame Elliott 40/extendSourceRect Elliott 16 0/shake Elliott 400/pause 300/showFrame Willy 16/extendSourceRect Willy 0 32/animate Haley true true 150 33 33 33 33 33 33 33 33 32 25 25 25 25 25 25 25 25 32 33 33 33 33 33 33 33 33 33 30 30 30 30 30 30 30 30 30 30 30 30 31 24 24 24 24 24 24 24 24 31 30 30 30 30 30 30 30 33/playMusic fallFest/playerControl iceFishing",
        "afterIceFishing_y2": "pause 100/playSound whistle/waitForOtherPlayers endContest/pause 1000/restoreStashedItem/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/extendSourceRect Pam reset/extendSourceRect Willy reset/extendSourceRect Elliott reset/specificTemporarySprite iceFishingCatch/faceDirection Pam 0/faceDirection Willy 3/faceDirection Elliott 1/playMusic event1/warpFarmers 71 35 0 72 35 0 70 35 0 69 35 0 73 35 0 71 36 0 70 36 0 72 36 0 69 36 0 73 36 0 left 73 37 0/pause 1000/viewport 71 35 true/pause 2000/move Lewis 0 4 2/speak Lewis \"Impressive, that's a lot of caught fish!$h / 真厉害，钓到了这么多鱼！$h\"/pause 300/showFrame Lewis 18/shake Lewis 1000/speak Lewis \"*gag*... I will never get used to that stench...$s / 呕……闻到这股腥味我就难受……$s\"/pause 500/showFrame Lewis 0/pause 600/move Lewis 0 1 2/speak Lewis \"Now, for the winner of this year's ice fishing competition... / 好了，本届冰钓比赛的胜利者是……\"/pause 800/playMusic none/pause 3000/cutscene iceFishingWinner/null/playMusic event1/pause 500/fork DickWin/move Lewis 0 1 2/speak Lewis \"Here's your prize! Enjoy. / 这是你的奖品！祝贺你。\"/awardFestivalPrize/null/move Lewis 0 -1 0/speak Lewis \"Well, that's it for this year's Festival of Ice. Thanks for coming, everyone! / 好了，今年的冰雪节到此为止！谢谢大家的光临！#$b#Now let's release these poor fish...$s / 现在快把那些可怜的鱼儿放生吧……$s\"/pause 500/faceDirection Lewis 3 true/pause 250/move Lewis -3 0 0 true/advancedMove Willy false 3 300 2 300 1 1000/advancedMove Pam false 4 100 3 150 -4 0 3 200 4 2000/advancedMove Elliott false 1 500 2 200 0 2 1 0 1 1000/pause 1000/viewport move 1 0 5000/pause 2000/playMusic none/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 1000/cutscene iceFishingWinnerMP/fork OtherPlayerWin/message \"I can't believe I won! Well, time to head home. / 我居然赢了！行了，该回家了。\"/waitForOtherPlayers festivalEnd/end",
        "DickWin_y2": "pause 100/jump Willy/pause 800/move Willy -3 0 0/speak Lewis \"Here's your prize, Willy. Enjoy. / 威利，这是你的奖品，祝贺你。\"/pause 500/move Willy 0 -1 0/move Lewis 1 0 2/move Lewis 0 1 2/playSound coin/pause 400/move Lewis 0 -1 0/pause 500/speak Lewis \"Well, that's it for this year's Festival of Ice. Thanks for coming, everyone! / 好了，今年的冰雪节到此为止！谢谢大家的光临！#$b#Now let's release these poor fish...$s / 现在快把那些可怜的鱼儿放生吧……$s\"/pause 500/faceDirection Lewis 3 true/pause 250/move Lewis -4 0 0 true/advancedMove Willy false 4 300 1 300 4 0 1 200 2 3000/advancedMove Pam false 4 100 3 150 -4 0 3 200 4 2000/advancedMove Elliott false 1 500 2 200 0 2 1 0 1 1000/pause 1000/viewport move 1 0 5000/pause 2000/playMusic none/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 1000/message \"I didn't win the competition, but it was still fun! Time to head home. / 我没有赢得比赛，但还是很好玩！该回家了。\"/waitForOtherPlayers festivalEnd/end",
        "Abigail_spouse_y2": "Imagine if we lived in an igloo together!$h / 如果咱们住在冰屋里面，肯定很快乐！$h#$e#It would be fun, but I'm happy living anywhere with you.$l / 不过只要有你，在哪里我都开心。$l",
        "Leah_spouse_y2": "Someday, I should teach you how to sculpt with ice! It would be fun!$h / 以后有机会的话，我教你做冰雕！很有趣的！$h#$e#I'd be very curious to see what you'd come up with. / 不知道你会做出什么呢。",
        "Maru_spouse_y2": "You'll do great out there, honey! Just stay calm and focused. / 亲爱的，只要保持冷静沉着就好，你可以的！",
        "Penny_spouse_y2": "When we get home, let's make a fire and have some hot cocoa.$0 / 我们回家之后生个火，弄点热可可喝吧。$0#$e#...with marshmallows?$h / ……再配上棉花糖怎么样？$h",
        "Haley_spouse_y2": "Come here, let me fix your hair... I'm going to take an action shot of you during the contest! / 来，我帮你整理一下发型……我准备在比赛的时候给你拍一张照片！",
        "Emily_spouse_y2": "Ta da! It's you! / 锵锵！这个是你！#$e#What? You don't see the resemblance? I think it's perfect! / 啊？你觉得不像？我觉得很完美啊！",
        "Sebastian_spouse_y2": "Hey, you really need to win the contest today.$0 / 哎，今天的比赛你一定要赢啊。$0#$e#Uh... well, I guess I made a little bet with Marlon...$1 / 呃……我好像跟马龙打了个小赌……$1",
        "Sam_spouse_y2": "You should teach me how to use a fishing rod sometime. I think I'd be good at it. / 你有空教教我怎么用鱼竿吧，我觉得我三两下就能学会。",
        "Alex_spouse_y2": "Hey! You're going to win by a longshot today, I know it. Make us proud! / 嘿！你今天肯定会脱颖而出，我相信你，加油！",
        "Harvey_spouse_y2": "Hi, honey. Good luck today in the ice fishing contest.$0 / 亲爱的，今天的冰钓比赛祝你好运。$0",
        "Elliott_spouse_y2": "I've been practicing my fishing technique. I won't hold back against you, my dear.$1 / 我已经练习钓鱼很久了，今天我可不会放水，亲爱的。$1",
        "Shane_spouse_y2": "Remember when we sat at the old pond and shared a beer? That was around here somewhere. / 你还记得当时我们坐在池塘边喝啤酒吗？就在这附近。#$e#Well, it's best not to dwell in the past... even the good memories bring me pain. / 唉，还是不要沉浸在过去了……即使是美好的回忆也会让我感到痛苦。",
        "Abigail_y2": "Have you ever thrown a bunch of pebbles on a frozen lake? It makes a very nice sound. / 你试过在结冰的湖面撒上一把鹅卵石吗？那个声音很好听。#$e#...Don't tell my dad, but I'm wearing the Winter Star sweater under this coat. / ……我跟你说，冬日之星的毛衣我穿在外套里面了，你别告诉我爸。",
        "Robin_y2": "Ice sculpting is a rewarding challenge for me. It's a distinct material that I'm not used to! / 做冰雕很困难，毕竟是我不熟悉的材料，但我觉得很开心！",
        "Demetrius_y2": "Water ice... a most profound substance, indeed. Necessary for life, it makes a fitting material for statuary meant to represent the living form. / 水、冰……确实是一种深奥的物质，本是生命之源，又可以用来做万物生灵的雕塑。",
        "Maru_y2": "The key to making a well-crafted snowman begins with ensuring a level foundation and avoiding excessive weight on the upper section.$3 / 想堆出结实的雪人是有诀窍的，一是要确保底部平整，二是要避免头部太重。$3",
        "Sebastian_y2": "You ever notice how quiet it is in the snow? / 大雪之中非常安静，你注意到了吗？",
        "Linus_y2": "Ahh... The forest has entered her long slumber for the winter...$1 / 啊……森林也开始了漫长的冬眠……$1",
        "Pierre_y2": "Our family has matching Winter Star sweaters. / 我给我们一家都准备了冬日之星的毛衣。#$e#Now, if only Abigail would wear hers...$2 / 要是阿比盖尔也能穿上就好了……$2",
        "Caroline_y2": "Hi, @. Are you finding any time to relax from your farming duties this winter?$0 / @，你好，今年冬天有没有闲下来一点？$0",
        "Alex_y2": "You think anyone would mind if I took a dip in the frozen lake after the festival? / 节日结束之后我想到结冰的湖里泡一会儿，你觉得怎么样？#$e#I've heard ice baths are good for the muscles. / 据说泡冰水对肌肉有好处。",
        "George_y2": "When you get old and bald like me, you need a good, warm hat. / 等你老了，头发掉光了，也会像我一样要戴暖和的帽子。",
        "Evelyn_y2": "You never know... this could be the last time I ever make a snowman with Alex. / 说不准这就是我最后一次跟亚历克斯堆雪人了……天知道呢。#$e#Life is short, dear. Make sure to treasure every moment. / 亲爱的，生命很短暂，一定要珍惜每一刻。",
        "Lewis_y2": "Hello, @. It's that time of the year again for the ice fishing festival. / @，你好，又到了一年一度的冰钓节了。#$b#Speak with me when you're ready to start the competition!$1 / 你准备好开始比赛的时候就来跟我说！$1",
        "Clint_y2": "These lumps of snow won't form into balls...$0 / 这几块雪就是捏不成雪球……$0#$e#I think I'm better working in the heat than in the cold.$2 / 我可能还是更擅长在炎热的环境干活。$2",
        "Penny_y2": "I'm too nervous to walk on the frozen lake... / 我不太敢在冰面上走。#$e#I read a book once, where a girl fell through the ice. / 我读过一本书，里面有个小女孩在冰面落水了。#$b#She was okay! But... I've been cautious about it ever since. / 她后来没事了！不过……从那时候开始我就特别小心。",
        "Pam_y2": "$y 'I lost last year because I chose a bad spot. I have a good feeling things will be different this time around._I don't think the location matters._Hah. Says you! I'll prove you wrong._I'll beat you anyway._...$4_Well, good luck._Same to you, kid.' / $y '我去年输了是因为我选的地方不好，我感觉今年会很顺利。_我觉得在哪里都一样。_呵，听你胡扯！我会证明你想错了。_无所谓，我会赢你的。_……$4_嗯，祝你好运。_祝你也好运，孩子。'",
        "Emily_y2": "A snowman has to look the part! Isn't the top hat and scarf stylish? / 雪人也要打扮得漂漂亮亮！这个礼帽和围巾是不是很时髦？",
        "Haley_y2": "I'm glad I wore earmuffs, it's freezing out here!$0 / 幸好我戴了耳罩，外面冷死了！$0#$e#I brought my camera this year. It's perfect lighting for a winter photoshoot! / 今年我带了相机，今天光线很好，适合拍冬天的照片！",
        "Jodi_y2": "Gatherings like this are a good way to build community with our neighbors. / 今天这种聚会可以促进邻里关系。#$e#It's nice how cold weather seems to bring people together. / 天一冷，大家好像就会聚在一起。",
        "Kent_y2": "You ready for the contest? We all think you're going to win. / 你做好比赛的准备了吗？我们一致觉得你会赢。",
        "Marlon_y2": "This time of year isn't so bad. No bugs during winter... / 冬天其实不算太糟糕，因为不会出现虫子……#$e#Think you can beat Willy this year? He's a tough competitor... / 今年你能超过威利吗？他很强……",
        "Sam_y2": "Hey, why are you laughing? He's not even done yet! / 哎，你笑什么？这雪人我还没堆完呢！#$e#You just wait... once we're finished, he'll be one fine snowman. / 你再等等……完工之后会很帅气的。",
        "Leah_y2": "You have to temper ice before cutting it, otherwise you can't shape it! / 雕刻冰之前要先让它温度升高一点，不然没法下刀！",
        "Shane_y2": "Winter can be really hard on animals. Did you install heaters in your coops and barns? / 冬天的时候，动物挺难熬的。你的栏舍和畜棚里装暖气片了吗？",
        "Marnie_y2": "Aww... That piggy looks adorable all bundled up!$1 / 哇……那只小猪裹得严严实实，好可爱！$1",
        "Elliott_y2": "Look here, it's my secret weapon... a flask of fine spirits, to wet my lips a moment before the whistle sounds... / 快看，这是我的秘密武器……一壶好酒，吹口哨之前先润一润嘴唇……",
        "Gus_y2": "I've been spending too much time holed up inside, watching Gridball... it's good to get outside in the crisp winter air. / 我在室内窝得太久了，一直在看格球比赛……寒冬里能到外面透透气也是很好的。",
        "Wizard_y2": "Hmm? How did you get here? / 嗯？你是怎么到这里来的？#$e#Pay no attention to me. I'm simply observing... / 不用管我，我就观察观察……",
        "Harvey_y2": "I shouldn't have waxed my moustache this morning, it's frozen solid! Oh dear...$2 / 早知道早上就不给胡子打蜡了，现在冻得硬邦邦！哎呦喂……$2#$e#Well, if you need an ice pick, you know where to find me...$h / 嗯，你需要碎冰锥的话，来找我就行……$h",
        "Jas_y2": "Don't the fish get cold under there?$3 / 鱼儿在下面不会冷吗？$3",
        "Vincent_y2": "My big brother is helping me build a snowman!$0 / 我哥哥在帮我堆雪人！$0",
        "Willy_y2": "Aye, the whole town'll be watchin' our little tournament today. Let's give them all a good show. / 嗐，今天镇上的人都来看我们的比赛，是时候大显身手了。",
        "Leo_y2": "*crunch* *crunch* Snow makes a funny noise when you step on it!$1 / （嘎吱嘎吱）踩在雪上的时候，会发出奇怪的声音！$1"
      }
    },
    {
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Festivals/winter25",
      "When": {
        "BilingualMode": "true"
      },
      "Entries": {
        "name": "Feast of the Winter Star / 冬日星盛宴",
        "Abigail_spouse": "I wonder if I could lick one of those canes... / 不知道能不能尝一尝那些甘蔗……",
        "Leah_spouse": "I'm thankful for our simple life on the farm.$h / 我很感恩现在过着的平凡生活。$h",
        "Maru_spouse": "Hey, @. I'm ready to head home whenever you are. / 嘿，@。我准备好回家了，就看你了。",
        "Penny_spouse": "I'm thankful to have met you...$l / 我很感恩在生命中遇到你……$l",
        "Haley_spouse": "Me?... Oh, I'm thankful for... how about I just show you when we get home tonight?$l / 我吗？……嗯，我很感恩……不如今晚到家后我再用行动告诉你吧？$l",
        "Sebastian_spouse": "Hey, @. As you can see, I'm fulfilling my family obligations... / 嘿，@。你没看见吗，我在履行我的家庭义务……",
        "Sam_spouse": "*yawn*... I'm here for the gifts and the cookies.$h / *哈欠*……我是为了这里的礼物和饼干才来的。$h",
        "Alex_spouse": "What am I thankful for? I'll show you when we get back home...$l / 我想感恩什么？等回到家后我会用行动告诉你……$l",
        "Harvey_spouse": "I'm feeling a little overwhelmed... thank goodness for this crisp air...$l / 我感觉有点惊慌失措……谢天谢地，这里的空气真清新……$l",
        "Elliott_spouse": "You don't need to get me anything, you've already given me the greatest gift of all...$l / 你不需要送我什么东西，你已经给了我最好的礼物……$l",
        "Abigail": "Nothing like a piping hot feast on a cold winter's day, huh?$h / 在寒冬中享用热气腾腾的食物，夫复何求啊？$h",
        "Robin": "Hiya, @. You're welcome to join our family table if you need company.$h / 嘿，@。你要是空虚寂寞冷的话，可以跟我们一家人一起吃饭啊。$h",
        "Demetrius": "I'll probably get another tool set this year... *sigh* / 看来今年是要破费买一套新工具了……*唉*",
        "Maru": "Hi, @.$h / 你好啊，@。$h",
        "Shane": "I've met some people who believe in spirits, and magic... but me? I've never seen anything that couldn't be explained by science. / 有人相信神明，有人相信魔法……至于我？我还从未见过科学解释不了的事情。",
        "Sebastian": "Spending time with family is tiring sometimes. / 跟家人在一起有时候是很累人的事。",
        "Pierre": "My sales figures have been phenomenal lately... thanks to the Feast of the Winter Star!$h / 我生意近来很红火……多亏了冬日星盛宴！$h#$e#Boy, holidays are good for business. I wonder if I could invent some new ones... / 小子，逢年过节总能赚得盆满钵满。要是我能发明些节日就好了……",
        "Caroline": "Ooohh... I've had too much nog.$h / 噢噢……我喝多了。$h",
        "Linus": "I'd join in... but I don't think I'm welcome.$s / 我会赴宴的……不过应该没有人会在乎。$s",
        "Alex": "Oh, hello.$s / 哦，你好。$s",
        "George": "A feast for some stupid star? Humbug! / 为天上的星星庆祝？有毛病！",
        "Evelyn": "Oh, my! Aren't you cold, dear? It's freezing! / 天啊！你不冷吗，亲？都要冻死我了！",
        "Lewis": "Today is a time to be thankful for this year's good fortune. Forget your worries for a day and relax! / 今天是庆祝今年大丰收的日子。暂时抛却一切烦恼，尽情去享乐吧！",
        "Clint": "*sigh*... All these happy families. But for me, just another lonely year. / *唉* ……羡煞旁人的家庭团聚。而我还是单身一人，好气哦。",
        "Emily": "$y '@! What are you hoping to find under the spirit tree?_A new watering can._All work and no play? That's not very fun.$s_A jug of spiced mead._Ooo... that sounds nice. Make sure to give me a taste.$h_A pair of stylish boots._I see. That would be a great gift!' / $y '@！你想在圣诞树下找到什么东西？_新的喷壶。_只用功不玩耍是很无聊的。$s_香料蜂蜜酒。_哟……很不错的样子。记得告诉我味道如何。$h_时尚的靴子。_哈，非常不错的礼物！'",
        "Penny": "What a beautiful tree.$h / 好美丽的树。$h",
        "Pam": "Hmmph... I'm still upset I didn't win the ice fishing competition.$4 / 唉……没有赢得冰钓比赛，我好难过。$4",
        "Haley": "I hope there's a new camera for me under the spirit tree! / 希望我的圣诞礼物是部相机！",
        "Jodi": "It's not a good time of year for a diet...$s / 此时此刻并非减肥的好日子……$s",
        "Kent": "Good afternoon, @. Happy Feasting. / 下午好，@。节日快乐。",
        "Sam": "I'm thankful for my guitar and my skateboard. Oh, and my family I guess. / 收到了吉他和滑板，感恩上帝。还有我的家人。",
        "Leah": "Gus was just telling me about his artisan candy canes. *yawn*$u / 格斯在跟我吹嘘他自己做的拐杖糖。*哈欠*$u#$e#I think he had too much cinnamon nog. / 我觉得他肉桂放多了。",
        "Marnie": "Welcome to the Feast of the Winter Star!$h / 欢迎来到冬日星盛宴！$h",
        "Elliott": "Why, hello @. It's chilly, isn't it? / 哈喽，@。天气好冷啊，对不？",
        "Gus": "It's a fine art, making candy canes. You've really got to search far and wide for the best ingredients. They aren't easy to come by these days!$h / 做糖拐杖是一门艺术。你得漫山遍野地寻找最适合的原料。这年头可难找了！$h#$e#I usually use Fern Island Ringfruit for my premier canes, you know. You can't beat that bright red coloring... And it's all natural! / 我通常用芬群岛果干做糖拐杖，这样才能保证质量。那亮丽的红色实在是太合适了……还是纯天然的！#$e#Oh, you want to know the secret to my deluxe double-canes? Okay, but you've got to promise absolute secrecy. *whisper* It's a drop of vanilla in the white candy to complement the cherry flavor.$h / 哦，你想知道制作顶级双拐杖糖的秘诀？告诉你可以，不过一定要保密啊。*细语*在白色果糖里面加入一点点香草，再与樱桃混合就行了。$h#$e#Of course, peppermint candy canes are the standard, and I always make a healthy batch of those as well. / 当然了，薄荷味拐杖糖也是很受欢迎的，所以我也会做很多这种口味的。#$e#Hey, you look like you're falling asleep. Are you okay?$s / 喂，你看起来快要睡着了。你没事吧？$s",
        "Willy": "$y 'Do you want to hear the Legend of the Winter Star?_Yes_In the night sky of winter, there is a bright star only visible from this valley. No one knows why this is... but in times of old people would come from far and wide to see it.*They believed that anyone who laid eyes on the Winter Star would be blessed with good fortune. Some even claim that the mysterious fruit known as =Stardrop is connected to the Winter Star in some way._No thanks_Suit yourself.' / $y '想不想听冬日星的传说？_想_在冬日的夜空中，有一颗闪亮的星星，只能从此谷中看见。没人知道为什么……在古时候，来自四面八方的人会聚集于此来看它。*他们相信看见星星的人会交上好运。甚至有人说被称为=星之果实的神秘水果是跟冬日星有某种程度的联系。_不用_那随你吧。'",
        "Wizard": "Ah, the mysterious Winter Star. One of the reasons I chose this valley as the location for my... research. / 啊，神秘的冬日星。它正是我选择此地进行……研究的原因之一。",
        "Harvey": "I'm thankful there were no medical emergencies this year! / 我很感恩今年没有人突发急症进医院！",
        "Sandy": "I heard it's raining back home. Is that why you came here?$h / 听说家乡在下雨。你是为避雨才跑来这里的吗？$h#$e#I kind of miss the rain, actually...$s / 话说我有点怀念雨景了……$s",
        "Jas": "Ohh! Presents!$h / 噢！好多礼物！$h",
        "Vincent": "Can we open presents now?! / 可以现在就打开吗？！",
        "Marlon": "Hey, good afternoon. / 嗨，下午好。",
        "Leo": "Linus feels uncomfortable about joining in, so I'm going to keep him company. / 莱纳斯感觉参加活动不太自在，所以我准备陪着他。#$e#We'll have our own little feast... mashed winter root and spice berry fish!$h / 我们打算自己举办一个小型宴会……会有冬根泥和香味浆果鱼！$h",
        "Abigail_spouse_y2": "Brr... It's cold! I wanna get back under the covers... / 嘶……冷死我了！我想马上钻回被窝里……",
        "Leah_spouse_y2": "Elliott's drinking too much cider again...$7 / 艾利奥特又喝太多苹果汁了……$7#$e#I'll come meet you at the table when I can find an exit... I'm starving! / 我想个办法脱身，然后去餐桌那里找你……我快饿死了！",
        "Maru_spouse_y2": "I'm thankful to have a loving family and you in my life...$0 / 能和你组成一个有爱的家庭，我很感激……$0",
        "Penny_spouse_y2": "I hope everyone likes my powdermelon crisp...$h / 我希望我做的霜瓜脆片大家都爱吃……$h",
        "Haley_spouse_y2": "When I count all the good things in my life, I feel like I've been blessed by the Winter Star. / 我的人生中遇到了太多美好的事情，感觉是被冬日之星祝福了。",
        "Emily_spouse_y2": "When Haley and I were kids, we always used to decorate cookies at this festival. / 小时候我跟海莉总是在这个节日上做装饰饼干。#$b#We should do it sometime! You can't let good traditions die out.$h / 我们哪次也试试看吧！美好的传统不能让它消失。$h",
        "Sebastian_spouse_y2": "Hey... don't worry, you don't need to get me anything.$h / 啊……别担心，你不用给我准备东西的。$h#$e#I'm just happy to wake up next to you every morning... what else could a guy ask for?$l / 每天早上醒来都有你在我身边……我还能要求什么呢？$l",
        "Sam_spouse_y2": "It's kinda fun watching everyone unwrap their presents... seeing their reactions.$h / 看每个人拆礼物的时候有不同的反应……还挺有趣的。$h#$e#Oh yeah, I got you something. I'll uhh... show you when we get back to the farmhouse!$10 / 对了，我给你准备了礼物。呃……等回家的时候再给你！$10",
        "Alex_spouse_y2": "Let me know if you get cold. I'll lend you my jacket.$0 / 如果你感觉冷的话跟我说，我的夹克衫给你穿。$0",
        "Harvey_spouse_y2": "There's a lot I'm thankful for, like my clinic, the good health of my patients... / 我有很多感激的事情，比如我的诊所，我的病人的身体健康……#$b#But ultimately, I'm most thankful for the life we're building together...$l / 不过我最感谢的还是我们一起创造的生活……$l",
        "Elliott_spouse_y2": "My dear, I require nothing at all on this day... you are already the greatest gift a man could hope for.$h / 亲爱的，今天我什么都不需要……你已经是我能得到的最好的礼物了。$h",
        "Shane_spouse_y2": "What am I thankful for? / 我感激的事情是什么？#$b#....uh...$3 / ……唔……$3#$b#I'm thankful... that you pulled me out of the gutter. And showed me that life is worth living.$6 / 我很感激……你把我从泥潭中拉出来，让我明白人生是值得过的。$6",
        "Abigail_y2": "I wonder which present is mine...$0 / 我想知道哪个礼物是给我的……$0#$e#I hope it's the big box!$h / 我希望是那个大盒子！$h",
        "Robin_y2": "Welp... Husband got me a new power saw this year...$6 / 嗐……我老公今年送了我一台新的电锯……$6#$b#He must've forgotten that he got me the same thing two years ago!$6 / 他肯定忘了，两年前他就送给我过了！$6",
        "Demetrius_y2": "Hmm... this green jelly has a minty flavor to it.$3 / 嗯……这个绿色的果冻有薄荷的味道。$3#$b#I wonder how mint became associated with the Feast Of The Winter Star? Does mint even grow in Winter?$3 / 我有点好奇，薄荷和冬日星盛宴是怎么搭上关系的？薄荷在冬天会长吗？$3",
        "Maru_y2": "It's pretty chilly today. Good thing everyone here is bundled up.$0 / 今天挺冷的，好在大家都穿得很暖和。$0",
        "Shane_y2": "One benefit of the cold weather is that I can put frozen pizzas under the tree. / 冷天有一个好处，就是我可以在树下放冷冻披萨。#$e#Someone's in for a real treat...$h / 能吃到好吃的了……$h",
        "Sebastian_y2": "I guess it's nice the whole family is together for once.$7 / 全家能聚在一起还挺好的。$7",
        "Pierre_y2": "Need any last minute gifts? I've got you covered! Take a look at my wares.$0 / 忘记买礼物了吗？我可以帮你搞定！来看看我的货。$0",
        "Caroline_y2": "Isn't the tree gorgeous?$h / 精灵树很漂亮吧？$h#$b#I spent all morning decorating it with Marnie and Jodi. It's a fun tradition! / 是我跟玛妮和乔迪花了一个早上装饰的。这是一项传统了，很快乐！",
        "Linus_y2": "The mayor personally invited me to his table. I couldn't turn that down! / 镇长亲自邀请我去他那桌，我无法拒绝！",
        "Alex_y2": "I'm pretty sure there's a gridball-shaped present with my name on it underneath the spirit tree.$1 / 我确信精灵树下有一个格球形状的礼物，上面写着我的名字。$1",
        "George_y2": "I already spend all day with the family, anyway. Why do we need a big hubbub out in the cold?$0 / 我本来就是一整天跟家里人在一起，为什么要大冷天跑出来吵吵闹闹？$0",
        "Evelyn_y2": "You are more than welcome to join us at our table, dear.$0 / 亲爱的，欢迎来我们桌一起吃东西。$0",
        "Lewis_y2": "Happy Feast Of The Winter Star, @.$h / @，祝你冬日星盛宴快乐。$h#$e#This is a time to unwind, enjoy good company, and express gratitude for all that we have.$0 / 趁着这个日子，可以放松身心、与人陪伴、表达我们的感激之情。$0",
        "Clint_y2": "I could use some new blacksmithing tools. Mine have gotten a little rusty over the years.$0 / 我该换新的打铁工具了，旧的用了这么多年有点生锈了。$0",
        "Emily_y2": "Look! It's the 'Winter Star'!%noturn$6 / 快看！是“冬日之星”！%noturn$6#$e#Oh, my mistake. It's just a decoration!$h / 啊，看错了，原来只是装饰！$h",
        "Penny_y2": "$y 'Hello, @. What kind of gift are you hoping to receive this year?_An iridium milk pail_Oh? I've never heard of such a thing. It sounds expensive._An interesting book_Yes, a book can make a very nice gift!$h_A lump of coal_...I can't tell if you're joking, but that could be a useful gift!$h' / $y '你好，@。你今年想收到什么礼物？_铱制挤奶桶_啊？我没听说过有这种东西，感觉会很贵。_有趣的书_不错啊，书是很好的礼物！$h_一块煤炭_……不知道你是不是在开玩笑，不过某种意义上确实挺实用的！$h'",
        "Pam_y2": "Mulled wine is the only thing keepin' me warm in this freezing weather!$h / 大冷天只有喝一杯热酒才能让我暖和起来！$h",
        "Haley_y2": "It's so pretty... I wish our town could always look like this!$0 / 好漂亮啊……我真希望小镇能一直是这个样子！$0",
        "Jodi_y2": "This spot is for the overflow presents. There's just too many to count this year!$0 / 这个位置是放多余礼物的。今年有太多的礼物了，数都数不过来！$0",
        "Kent_y2": "Seeing my little boy happy and healthy is what I'm thankful for.$h / 能看到儿子健康快乐，我很感激。$h",
        "Sam_y2": "Who gifts someone a Joja basket?...$2 / 谁会给别人送 Joja 篮子啊？……$2",
        "Leah_y2": "Sometimes I dread going to parties, but afterwards I'm always glad I went! / 有时候我真的不敢去参加派对，但去了之后还是感觉很高兴的！",
        "Marnie_y2": "Happy Feasting, @!$1 / 祝你宴会快乐，@！$1",
        "Elliott_y2": "*urp*$8 / 嗝！$8#$b#Ahh... excuse me. Where are my manners? This spiced cider has quite a potent fizz to it.$4 / 啊……对不起，我有点丢脸。这个香料苹果汁的气很足。$4",
        "Gus_y2": "Eat! Eat, while it's still fresh and hot.$0 / 吃吧！趁还新鲜热乎。$0#$e#I could go on and on about my new method of making candy canes... but I'll spare you the details this year!$1 / 我是挺想跟你仔细说说制作拐杖糖的新方法……不过今年就不说那些细枝末节了！$1",
        "Willy_y2": "I'm a simple man, @... I'm thankful for a solid roof over me head, and a hot can o' beans in the mornin'!$h / @，我的生活要求不高……有遮风挡雨的屋子，早饭有一罐热乎的豆子我就满足了！$h",
        "Wizard_y2": "Ah, the mysterious Winter Star. One of the reasons I chose this valley as the location for my... research. / 啊，神秘的冬日之星。因为这个我才选择在星露谷进行我的……研究。不过只是一个原因。",
        "Harvey_y2": "Have you tried the pecan pie? It's my favorite.$0 / 你尝过山核桃派了吗？我最喜欢了。$0",
        "Jas_y2": "Is it time to open presents yet?$0 / 现在可以拆礼物了吗？$0",
        "Vincent_y2": "I got the toy dinosaur I wanted! See!?$1 / 我收到我想要的玩具恐龙了！快看！！$1#$e#It's called um... a ste-...stego-...stegosonaurus! ...I think.$0 / 好像是叫……剑龙？我没记错吧。$0",
        "Marlon_y2": "Hmm? Oh, hello.$0 / 嗯？哦，你好。$0#$e#Don't pay any mind to me. Go enjoy yourself.  / 不用管我，自己去玩吧。",
        "Leo_y2": "I don't know what most of this stuff is... but it tastes good!$0 / 我不知道这些东西大部分是什么……但是味道很好！$0"
      }
    }
  ]
}